A हिमानी गुफा is a cave formed within the बर्फ of a glacier.
हिमानी गुफाएं हैं प्रायः पुकारा ice गुफाएं, but इस term is properly प्रयुक्त to describe bedrock गुफाएं that contain year-round बर्फ.
in भौतिकी, गोलाकार गति is a movement of an ऑब्जेक्ट along the circumference of a वृत्त or rotation साथ a circular पाथ.
it can be uniform, साथ constant angular रेट of rotation ( और निरंतर गति ), or non-uniform साथ a बदलना rate of रोटेशन.
the rotation around a फिक्स्ड axis of a three-dimensional body involves circular गति of इसके भाग.
the equations of गति describe the movement of the center of द्रव्यमान of a देह.
उदाहरण of गोलाकार गति शामिल : an कृत्रिम satellite orbiting the Earth at निरंतर ऊँचाई, a स्टोन जिससे is tied to a rope and is being swung in वृत्त, a car turning through a वक्र in a race track, an इलेक्ट्रॉन चलती लम्बवत to a वर्दी चुम्बकीय field, and a गियर turning inside a mechanism.
Since the ऑब्जेक्ट 's गति वेक्टर is constantly changing direction, the चलती ऑब्जेक्ट is undergoing त्वरण by a centripetal force in the दिशा of the बीच of रोटेशन.
बगैर this त्वरण, the object होता move in a सीधा लकीर, according to Newton 's laws of गति.

In the संयुक्त राज्य, the title of संघीय न्यायधीश प्रायः means a न्यायधीश नियुक्त by the अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य और confirmed by the संयुक्त राज्य सीनेट pursuant to the Appointments Clause in आलेख II of the संयुक्त राज्य Constitution.
In जोड to the परम् अदालत of the United राज्य, जिनकी existence और some aspects of whose क्षेत्राधिकार are परे the constitutional शक्ति of कॉंग्रेस to alter, अधिनियमों of कॉंग्रेस have स्थापित 13 न्यायालयों of appeals ( भी पुकारा `` circuit courts '' ) with appellate jurisdiction over अलग regions of the संयुक्त States, and 94 संयुक्त राज्य ज़िला न्यायालयों.
Every न्यायधीश नियुक्त to ऐसे a court may be categorized as a संघीय judge ; such स्थितियाँ शामिल the Chief Justice और संबद्ध justices of the परम् अदालत, सर्किट Judges of the courts of appeals, and ज़िला न्यायाधीशों of the संयुक्त राज्य district न्यायालयों.
All of these judges वर्णित यूँ far हैं referred to sometimes as `` आलेख iii judges '' because वे कसरत the judicial शक्ति vested in the judicial branch of the संघीय government by आलेख iii of the u.S. संविधान.
in जोड, judges of the Court of International व्यापार exercise judicial शक्ति pursuant to आलेख III.

परिवर्तनीय Universal जीवन बीमे ( प्रायः shortened to VUL ) is a प्रकार of जीवन insurance that builds a नकदी value.
in a vul, the नकदी value can be invested in a wide किस्में of पृथक accounts, similar to परस्पर funds, and the choice of जिससे of the उपलब्धियाँ separate accounts to use is entirely up to the अनुबंध owner.
the 'variable ' घटक in the नाम refers to इस ability to invest in पृथक accounts whose मान vary—they vary because वे हैं invested in भण्डार and/or bond बाज़ार.
The 'universal ' component in the नाम refers to the flexibility the मालिक रै in बनाना प्रीमियम payments.
the premiums can vary इससे nothing in a दिए month up to maximums पारिभाषित by the आतंरिक आय कोड लिये जीवन insurance.
इस flexibility is in कंट्रास्ट to whole life insurance that रै fixed प्रीमियम payments कि typically can नहीं be छूटी बगैर lapsing the नीति ( although एक may exercise an स्वचालित Premium ऋण feature, or surrender dividends to pay a Whole जीवन प्रीमियम ).
Variable सार्वभौमिक life is a प्रकार of स्थाई life बीमे, क्युकी the मौत benefit होगा be सशुल्क if the insured मरता कोई समय as long as there is sufficient cash मान to अदा the लागत of बीमे in the नीति.
With सबसे if not सब VULs, नापसंद पूरे जीवन, वहीँ is no endowment आयु ( the age at जिससे the नकदी मान बराबरी the मौत लाभ राशि, which लिये whole जीवन is typically 100 ).
इस is yet another key advantage of vul over पूरे जीवन.
साथ a ठेठ पूरे life नीति, the death benefit is limited to the face राशि निर्दिष्ट in the नीति, और at endowment age, the face राशि is all कि is paid आउट.
Thus with either death or endowment, the insurance कम्पनी keeps कोई cash value निर्मित up over the सालो.
however, कुछ participating पूरे life policies प्रस्ताव riders which specify कि any dividends सशुल्क on the नीति be प्रयुक्त to खरीदें `` paid up परिवर्धन '' to the नीति जिससे बढ़ाएँ both the नकदी मान और the death लाभ over समय.
if investments बना in the separate खाते out-perform the सामान्य खाता of the बीमे company, a उच्चतर rate-of-return can occur than the फिक्स्ड rates-of-return ठेठ for पूरे जीवन.
The संयोजन over the सालो of no endowment आयु, continually increasing death लाभ, और if a ऊँची rate-of-return is earned in the पृथक accounts of a VUL policy, this could परिणाम in higher value to the owner or लाभार्थी than कि of a पूरे जीवन policy साथ the same amounts of money सशुल्क in as प्रीमियम.

purdue विश्वविद्यालयों, located in West lafayette, इंडियाना, is the फ्लैगशिप university of the six-campus purdue विश्वविद्यालयों प्रणाली.
Purdue was संस्थापित on may 6, 1869, as a land-grant विश्वविद्यालयों जब the इंडियाना सामान्य सभा, लेने advantage of the morrill अधिनियम, accepted a दान of जमीन और money इससे lafayette businessman जॉन Purdue to establish a कॉलेज of science, प्रौद्योगिकी, और कृषि in his नाम.
the पहला classes यहूद आयोजित on सितंबर 16, 1874, with six instructors और 39 विद्यार्थी.
आज, purdue is a member of the बिग टेन सम्मेलन, और is a well ज्ञात world-class research संस्था.
purdue enrolls the दूसरी largest छात्र देह of कोई विश्वविद्यालयों in इंडियाना as well as the fourth largest अंतरराष्ट्रीय student population of कोई university in the संयुक्त राज्य.
Purdue offers दोनो undergraduate और ग्रैजुएट कार्यक्रम in over 211 major areas of पढ़ाई, and is well ज्ञात for its competitive engineering curricula.
The university रै भी महरूम highly influential in America 's history of विमानन, having established the पहला कॉलेज क्रेडिट offered in flight प्रशिक्षण, the first four-year bachelor 's degree in विमानन, and the first विश्वविद्यालयों विमानक्षेत्र ( purdue विश्वविद्यालयों Airport ).
Purdue 's विमानन प्रौद्योगिकी कार्यक्रम remains एक of the सबसे competitive aviation-specific कार्यक्रम in the world.
in the mid-20th सदी, Purdue 's विमानन कार्यक्रम विस्तारित to encompass उन्नत spaceflight प्रौद्योगिकी giving rise to purdue 's उपनाम, Cradle of astronauts.
twenty-three Purdue graduates have गए on to become astronauts, including गस Grissom ( एक of the असली पारा सात astronauts ), Neil आर्मस्ट्रांग ( the पहला person to चलना on the moon ), and यूजीन cernan ( the most हाल व्यक्ति to चलना on the चंद्रमा ).
a sebaceous गाँठ ( ) is a term कि loosely refers to either epidermoid cysts ( भी ज्ञात as epidermal cysts ; L72.0 ) or पिलर cysts ( also ज्ञात as trichilemmal cysts ; l72.1 ).
क्युकी an epidermoid गाँठ originates in the epidermis और a pilar गाँठ originates इससे बाल follicles, by परिभाषा, neither प्रकार of cyst is सख्ती a sebaceous cyst.
the name is regarded as a misnomer as the वसीय, white, semi-solid सामग्री in both of these गाँठ entities is not sebum, लकिन keratin.
Furthermore, under the microscope neither एंटिटी contains वसामय glands.
in practice, however, the शर्तें हैं often used interchangeably.
`` सच्चा '' sebaceous cysts हैं relatively rare और are known as steatocystomas or, if अनेक, as steatocystoma मल्टीप्लेक्स.

a pointe जूता is a प्रकार of जूता worn by बैले dancers जब performing pointe कार्य.

वे हैं normally worn by मादा dancers, हालांकि पुरूष नर्तक may पहनें them लिये अपरंपरागत roles ऐसे as the भद्दा stepsisters in Cinderella, नीचे in A midsummer Night 's Dream, or मेन performing as महिलाओं in dance कंपनियाँ such as लेस नाटिकाओं Trockadero and grandiva.
वे हैं manufactured in a किस्में of रंगों, most commonly in शेड्स of light गुलाबी.
इस tablespoon रै a क्षमता of परिचय 15 ml.
Measuring spoons
in the us and parts of कनाडा, a tablespoon is the largest प्रकार of चमचा used for eating from a कटोरी.
in the uk, Europe और most राष्ट्रमंडल देशों, a tablespoon is a type of large चमचा प्रायः प्रयुक्त for सेवारत.
in देशों जहाँ a tablespoon is a सेवारत spoon, the निकटतम equivalent to the us tablespoon is either the मिठाई spoon or the soup चमचा.
a tablespoonful, nominally the capacity of one tablespoon, is commonly प्रयुक्त as a measure of volume in cooking.
it is abbreviated as T, tb, tbs, tbsp, tblsp, or tblspn.
the capacity of ordinary tablespoons is नहीं regulated by law and is विषय to considerable variation.
in the USA one tablespoon ( measurement ईकाई ) is approximately 15 mL ; the capacity of an actual tablespoon ( dining utensil ) ranges इससे 7 mL to 14 mL.
In ऑस्ट्रेलिया एक tablespoon ( मापन ईकाई ) is 20 mL.

A rocket engine, or simply `` प्रक्षेपास्त्र '', is a jet इंजन कि uses only भंडारित propellant द्रव्यमान for forming its high गति propulsive जेट.
Rocket engines are प्रतिक्रिया इंजन and obtain thrust in accordance साथ न्यूटन 's तीसरा विधि.
चूंकि वे need no बाह्य सामग्री to form उनके जेट, प्रक्षेपास्त्र इंजन can be प्रयुक्त for spacecraft नोदन as well as स्थलीय उपयोग, such as मिसाइलें.
सबसे प्रक्षेपास्त्र engines हैं आतंरिक combustion इंजन, हालांकि non-combusting फ़ॉर्म भी exist.
प्रक्षेपास्त्र इंजन as a समूह have the उच्चतम exhaust गतियाँ, हैं by far the lightest, but हैं the तनिक propellant कुशल of all types of jet engines.

हैजा is an संक्रमण in the small intestine caused by the bacterium Vibrio cholerae.

the अनोखा tells of a यंग man named डोरियन धूसर, the subject of a painting by artist बेसिल Hallward.

Chronic obstructive pulmonary बीमारी ( copd ), भी ज्ञात as दीर्घकालिक obstructive फेफड़ों बीमारी ( ठंडा ), दीर्घकालिक obstructive airway बीमारी ( COAD ), दीर्घकालिक airflow limitation ( कैलोरी ) and दीर्घकालिक obstructive respiratory disease ( cord ), is the occurrence of दीर्घकालिक ब्रोंकाइटिस or emphysema, a जोड़ी of commonly co-existing diseases of the lungs in which the एयरवेज़ सीमित over समय.
इस हद airflow to और इससे the फेफड़े, causing shortness of breath ( dyspnea ).
in clinical practice, copd is defined by इसके characteristically कम airflow on फेफड़ों फलन tests.
In कंट्रास्ट to दमा, इस limitation is poorly reversible and प्रायः gets progressively बदतर over time.
copd is caused by noxious particles or गैस, सबसे commonly इससे तम्बाकू smoking, जिससे triggers an abnormal inflammatory जवाब in the lung.
The diagnosis of copd requires lung function tests.
Important management रणनीति are smoking cessation, vaccinations, पुनर्वास, और ड्रग therapy ( often using inhalers ).
कुछ patients go on to require long-term ऑक्सीजन चिकित्सा or lung प्रत्यारोपण.
Worldwide, copd क्रमित as the छठे अग्रणी कारण of मौत in 1990.
It is प्रक्षिप्त to become the चौथी अग्रणी cause of मौत worldwide by 2030, due to an बढ़ाएँ in smoking दरों और जनसांख्यिकी परिवर्तन in अनेक देशों.
COPD is the third अग्रणी कारण of death in the u.S., और the economic बोझ of copd in the u.S. in 2007 थी $ 42.6 billion in स्वास्थ्य परवाह costs and खोया उत्पादकता.

deepwater खुदाई is the process of आयल और गैस खोजी और उत्पादन in depths of more than 500 फीट.
By this परिभाषा, there हैं लगभग 600 deepwater कुएं in the Gulf of मैक्सिको.
it has महरूम economically infeasible लिये many सालो, but साथ उठती oil prices, अधिक कंपनियाँ are निवेश in this क्षेत्रफल.
प्रमुख कंपनियाँ working in this sector शामिल Diamond Offshore, TransOcean, and Baker ह्यूजेस.
There हैं basically two kinds of मोबाईल deepwater drilling rigs : semi-submersible खुदाई rigs and drillships.
खुदाई can also be performed from a fixed-position installation ऐसे as a फ्लोटिंग spar ( मंच ) or tension-leg platform.
Recent उद्योग विश्लेषण रै अनुमानित that the total expenditure in the वैश्विक deepwater infrastructure मार्केट होगा पहुँचें $ 145bn in 2011.
“Not सब आयल is accessible on जमीन or in उथले जल.
तुम can ढूँढें कुछ आयल जमा दफ्न गहन अंतर्गत the समंदर floor.”... using sonic उपकरण, आयल companies determine the खुदाई साइट सबसे likely to उपज आयल.
तब वे use a मोबाईल offshore drilling ईकाई ( मोदू ) to खुदाई the आरंभिक खूब.
Some इकाई हैं परिवर्तित into उत्पादन rigs, meaning they स्विच from खुदाई लिये आयल to capturing oil once it 's मिला.
सबसे of the time, the oil कम्पनी will replace the मोदू with a अधिक स्थाई आयल production रिग to कैप्चर oil.”... The मोदू 's जॉब is to ड्रिल bas into the ocean 's मंजिल to ढूँढें आयल deposits.
the part of the ड्रिल that extends below the deck और through the जल is पुकारा the riser.
the riser allows for खुदाई fluids to मूव between the मंजिल and the rig.
इंजीनियर्स निम्नतर a ड्रिल string -- a श्रेणी of pipes designed to ड्रिल bas to the आयल deposit -- through the riser.”
“the विस्तार of deepwater खुदाई is happening despite दुर्घटनाओं in offshore फ़ील्ड... ”
in 2010 a large विस्फोट occurred killing 11 workers और spilling लाखो of गैलन of oil into the गल्फ of मैक्सिको जबकि a BP oil रिग थी drilling in deep waters.
“... despite the risks, the deepwater खुदाई trend is spreading in the भूमध्यसागरीय and बंद the coast of ईस्ट अफ़्रीकी after a string of विशाल discoveries of प्राकृतिक gas.”
“The कारण लिये the resumption of ऐसे drilling, analyst say, is continuing high माँग for उर्जा worldwide.”
America needs the आयल so it is almost necessary to face the ऊँची risks कि come with deepwater drilling in अनुक्रम लिये अमेरिकी to continue to carry on their रोज जीवनदान.
“the उर्जा विभाग recently projected कि गल्फ आयल उत्पादन होता विस्तार इससे इसके 2011 स्तर of 1.3 लाख barrels a day, still nearly a क्वार्टर of कुल घरेलू production, to 2 लाख barrels a day by 2020.”
deepwater खुदाई affects the environment in दोनो negative and धनात्मक ways.
हालांकि deepwater खुदाई rarely कल्याणकारी आयल spills it is still a hazardous संभावित निष्कर्ष.

On the अन्य hand deepwater खुदाई प्रभाव the environment in a positive ways too.

a फर्न is कोई एक or अधिक of a समूह of परिचय 12,000 प्रजाति of पौधे belonging to the वनस्पति समूह ज्ञात as pteridophyta.
Unlike mosses, they have जाइलम and फ्लोएम ( making them vascular पौधे ).
वे have stems, leaves, and roots जैसे other vascular पौधे.
ferns reproduce via बीजाणुओं और have neither बीज nor पुष्प.
by दूर the largest समूह of ferns is the leptosporangiate ferns, but ferns as defined here ( भी पुकारा monilophytes ) शामिल horsetails, whisk ferns, marattioid ferns, और ophioglossoid ferns.
the term pteridophyte also refers to ferns और a few अन्य बीजरहित vascular पौधे ( see वर्गीकरण खण्ड नीचे ).
Ferns पहला appear in the fossil record 360 million सालो पहले in the Carboniferous लकिन अनेक of the वर्तमान परिवारों और species किया नहीं appear until roughly 145 million सालो पहले in the जल्दी cretaceous ( बाद flowering पौधे came to dominate many environments ).
ferns are not of प्रमुख आर्थिक महत्व, लकिन कुछ are grown or gathered लिये खाना, as शोभायमान plants, लिये remediating contaminated soils, और have महरूम the subject of research लिये their क्षमता to हटाएँ some रासायनिक pollutants from the air.
कुछ are significant weeds.
They also खेल a भूमिका in mythology, आयुर्विज्ञान, and आर्ट.
चपटा roofs in Israel
Flat छत in Los Angeles
a चपटा छत is a प्रकार of covering लिये a भवन.
in कंट्रास्ट to the अधिक sloped रूप of roof, a चपटा roof is horizontal or nearly आड़ा.
the slope of a roof is properly known as its pitch : roofs जिससे are nearly flat are ज्ञात as low-pitch roofs ( as the कोण of slope increases, so the pitch is said to increase ).
Any sheet of material प्रयुक्त to कवर a चपटा or low-pitched roof is प्रायः known as a झिल्ली और the प्राथमिक purpose of these झिल्लियों is to waterproof the छत area.
सामग्री that cover flat roofs typically allow the water to run बंद इससे a slight inclination or camber into a gutter प्रणाली.
Water from some चपटा roofs such as on garden sheds sometimes बहती freely बंद the edge of a roof, though gutter प्रणालियों हैं of advantage in keeping दोनो दीवारें और मूलाधार शुष्क.
ड्रेनेज on smaller roofs often lead जल directly onto the मैदान, or better, into a विशेषकर बना soakaway.
Gutters on larger roofs प्रायः सीसे water into the rainwater नाले प्रणाली of any built up क्षेत्रफल.
Occasionally flat roofs हालांकि हैं designed to collect जल in a पूल, प्रायः for aesthetic purposes, or लिये rainwater buffering.
Flat roofs मौजूद सब over the संसार and each area रै इसके own परंपरा or preference for materials प्रयुक्त.
in warmer climes where वर्षा is कम और जमने is unlikely to occur, अनेक चपटा roofs हैं बस built of masonry or concrete और इस is शुभ at keeping out the ऊष्मा of the सूर्य and सस्ती और आसान to build where timber is नहीं readily उपलब्धियाँ.
In क्षेत्रों जहाँ the छत could become saturated by बरसात और लीक, or where water soaked into the brickwork could फ्रीज to बर्फ और thus सीसे to 'blowing ' ( breaking up of the mortar/brickwork/concrete by the विस्तार of ice as it फ़ॉर्म ) ये roofs are नहीं suitable.
Traditionally सबसे चपटा roofs in the western संसार मेक use of तारकोल or more usually तारकोल पेपर लागू over roof decking to keep a building watertight.
The tar or tarpaper is in फेरे covered in gravel to रखना the सूर्य 's heat, UV किरणें और weather बंद it और helps protect it इससे cracking or blistering and degradation.
छत decking is usually of plywood, chipboard or osb boards ( osb = उन्मुख strand फलक, भी ज्ञात as स्टर्लिंग board ) of around 18mm thickness.
The tar कोटिंग is applied in एक or more coats as a hot द्रव, heated in a तारकोल kettle, or as sheets of tar impregnated 'paper ' glued bas और sealed साथ at joints by hot तारकोल - once it रै cooled, the बजरी is स्प्रेड evenly over it.
a प्रमुख कारण लिये failure of ये traditional roofs is ignorance or lack of मेंटेनेंस where लोगों or events कारण the बजरी to be moved or removed इससे the तारकोल or tarpaper waterproofing, यूँ exposing it to मौसम and sun whereupon cracking and blistering occurs over time and आखिरकार water gets in.
Tarpaper is usually a 'paper ' or fibre material soaked or impregnated in तारकोल.
as बजरी can not protect tarpaper सतहों जहाँ they वृद्धि खड़ा इससे the छत such as on मुंडेर walls or upstands, tarpaper विसंगतियाँ हैं produced साथ ठीक बजरी applied to the hot tar दौरान the प्रक्रम of manufacture ऐसे that a स्थाई layer of gravel is stuck to it in अनुक्रम to दे it ongoing सुरक्षा.
tarpapers vary in विशेषता as करता the कारीगरी और training of those applying it to उपज अधिक or less कामयाब results.
in कुछ सूक्ष्म climates or छायांकित areas these बल्कि 'basic ' tarpaper roofs can पिछला खूब in संबंध to the cost of सामग्री खरीदें और लागत of laying them, however the cost of modern membranes such as epdm has आइये bas over हाल सालो to मेक उन्हें more and अधिक सस्ती.
वहीँ हैं now more firms supplying modern विकल्प और वहीँ is generally a growing जागरूकता of उनके प्रदर्शन और availability.
If a leak करता occur on a चपटा छत तब क्षति प्रायः goes unnoticed लिये long अवधि of time दौरान जिससे जल penetrates और soaks the अलंकार and any insulation and/or structure beneath it.
This can lead to महंगी क्षति इससे the rot जिससे प्रायः develops and if बाएँ can weaken the छत ढांचा.
वहीँ हैं भी various स्वास्थ्य risks to लोगों and पशु breathing the सांचे spores : the गंभीरता of इस स्वास्थ्य risk remains a debated पाइंट.
एक प्रॉब्लम with maintaining flat roofs is that if water करता penetrate the अवरोध covering ( be it परंपरागत or a आधुनिक membrane ) it can travel a long रास्ता पहले causing visible damage or टपकती into a building जहाँ it can be seen.
यूँ it is not आसान to see where it is टपकती in order to मरम्मत it.
एकबार underlying छत अलंकार is soaked it प्रायः sags causing a further संग्रहण or puddling of water in कि क्षेत्रफल और the प्रॉब्लम worsens.
a cd-rom ( ) is a pre-pressed कॉम्पैक्ट डिस्क which contains data.
the नाम is an एक्रोनिम जिससे स्टैंड for `` कॉम्पैक्ट डिस्क read-only मेमोरी ``.
Computers can read CD-ROMs, लकिन can नहीं write on उन्हें.
cd-roms are popularly प्रयुक्त to वितरित computer software, सहित वीडियो खेल और मल्टीमीडिया applications, हालांकि कोई data can be भंडारित ( up to the capacity limit of a डिस्क ).
कुछ cds, पुकारा उन्नत cds, थाम both कंप्यूटर आंकड़ा और ऑडियो साथ the latter capable of being played on a CD खिलाड़ी, जबकि data ( ऐसे as तन्त्र or digital video ) is only usable on a computer ( such as आईएसओ 9660 स्वरूप pc cd-roms ).
the Yellow किताब is the तकनीकी मानक कि defines the स्वरूप of cd-roms.
एक of a set of color-bound books कि contain the technical विशेषताएँ लिये सब cd स्वरुप, the Yellow किताब, निर्मित by Sony और फिलिप्स, was the first एक्सटेंशन of कॉम्पैक्ट डिस्क Digital ऑडियो.
it adapted the स्वरूप to hold कोई रूप of आंकड़ा.
Joanne `` jo '' Rowling ( ), ( born 31 July 1965 ), कलम name J. K. Rowling, is a British novelist, बेहतरीन ज्ञात as the लेखक of the हैरी कुम्हार fantasy श्रेणी.
The कुम्हार books have gained विश्वव्यापी ध्यान, won multiple awards, और बेची अधिक than 400 लाख copies.
They have become the best-selling किताब श्रेणी in history, और महरूम the आधार for a श्रेणी of films which has become the highest-grossing फिल्मी श्रेणी in इतिहास.
रोलिंग था overall स्वीकृति on the स्क्रिप्ट as खूब as maintaining creative कंट्रोल by सेवारत as a निर्माता on the फाइनल किस्त.
born in yate, ग्लॉस्टरशायर, रोलिंग थी working as a researcher और bilingual सचिव लिये माफ़ी अंतरराष्ट्रीय जब वो conceived the विचार for the Harry कुम्हार series on a विलम्बित train इससे मैनचेस्टर to London in 1990.
the seven-year period कि followed entailed the death of उसके माँ, तलाक इससे उसके पहला husband and गरीबी until Rowling समाप्त the first novel in the श्रेणी, हैरी कुम्हार and the पारस 's Stone ( 1997 ).
Rowling subsequently प्रकाशित 6 sequels—the पिछला, हैरी कुम्हार और the Deathly hallows ( 2007 ) —as खूब as 3 पूरक to the series.
In 2012, रोलिंग parted साथ her एजेंसी and resumed लिखने in the रूप of a tragicomedy अनोखा aimed at वयस्क readership, हकदार the Casual रिक्ति.
रोलिंग रै said वो is फिलहाल working on दो books—one aimed लिये वयस्कों, the अन्य for children younger than the Harry Potter दर्शक, और वो expects the latter to be प्रकाशित पहला.
रोलिंग has led a `` rags to riches `` जीवन स्टोरी, in which she progressed from living on state लाभ to multi-millionaire status within पाँच years.
वो is the United किंगडम 's best-selling author since रिकॉर्ड began, साथ sales in excess of £238m.
the 2008 Sunday टाइम्स समृद्ध सूची अनुमानित Rowling 's सौभाग्य at £560 लाख ( $ 798 लाख ), रैंकिंग उसके as the बारहवीं richest स्त्री in the संयुक्त Kingdom.
Forbes क्रमित Rowling as the forty-eighth सबसे शक्तिशाली हस्ती of 2007, and TIME पत्रिका नामित उसके as a runner-up लिये its 2007 Person of the Year, noting the social, moral, and political प्रेरणा she रै given उसके प्रशंसक.
in अक्तूबर 2010, Rowling थी नामित the `` Most influential स्त्री in Britain '' by अग्रणी पत्रिका editors.
She has become a notable लोकसेवक, supporting ऐसे charities as Comic Relief, एक जनक Families, Multiple Sclerosis Society of Great ब्रिटेन और lumos ( formerly the Children 's High स्तर Group ).

the eye, eyewall, and surrounding rainbands, विशेषताएँ of तीव्र cyclones, are clearly दृश्य in इस view इससे space.
a तीव्र cyclone is a तूफ़ान प्रणाली characterized by a low-pressure बीच घिरी by a spiral व्यवस्था of thunderstorms कि produce दमदार winds और heavy बरसात.
Tropical cyclones strengthen जब water काफूर from the ocean is released as the saturated एयर उदय, resulting in condensation of water वाष्प contained in the moist air.
वे are fueled by a different ऊष्मा यांत्रिकी than अन्य cyclonic windstorms ऐसे as nor'easters, European windstorms, and ध्रुवीय lows.
the characteristic कि separates तीव्र cyclones इससे other cyclonic systems is that at कोई ऊँचाई in the atmosphere, the center of a tropical चक्रवात will be warmer than its परिवेश ; a घटना called `` गरम core `` तूफ़ान systems.
the term `` तीव्र '' refers दोनो to the भौगोलिक उत्पत्ति of ये प्रणालियों, which प्रायः रूप in तीव्र regions of the globe, और to their गठन in maritime तीव्र एयर masses.
the पद `` चक्रवात '' refers to such तूफ़ान ' cyclonic प्रकृति, साथ counterclockwise हवा प्रवाह in the Northern गोलार्ध और clockwise हवा प्रवाह in the Southern गोलार्ध.
The opposite दिशा of the wind flow is a परिणाम of the कॉरिऑलिस फ़ोर्स.
Depending on its location और शक्ति, a तीव्र cyclone is referred to by names such as hurricane (, ), तूफ़ान ( ), तीव्र तूफ़ान, cyclonic तूफ़ान, तीव्र अवसाद, and बस चक्रवात.
जबकि tropical cyclones can produce extremely शक्तिशाली हवाएँ और मूसलाधार rain, वे हैं भी able to produce high लहरें, damaging तूफ़ान surge, और tornadoes.
They develop over large लाशें of warm water, and खोना their strength if they मूव over land due to increased सतह घर्षण and loss of the गरम ocean as an उर्जा सोर्स.
इस is why तटीय regions can प्राप्त significant damage इससे a tropical चक्रवात, जबकि inland regions हैं relatively सुरक्षित from receiving strong winds.
Heavy rains, however, can उपज significant बाढ़ inland, और तूफ़ान surges can produce extensive तटीय बाढ़ up to from the तटरेखा.
Although उनके effects on human populations can be devastating, तीव्र cyclones can relieve सूखा शर्तें.
वे also carry ऊष्मा उर्जा दूर from the tropics and हस्तांतरण it toward शीतोष्ण latitudes, which makes them an महत्वपूर्ण भाग of the वैश्विक वायुमंडलीय circulation यांत्रिकी.
As a परिणाम, tropical cyclones help to maintain संतुलन in the धरती 's क्षोभमण्डल, और to maintain a अपेक्षाकृत stable and गरम temperature worldwide.
अनेक तीव्र cyclones develop when the वायुमंडलीय conditions around a कमजोर disturbance in the माहौल हैं favorable.
The पृष्ठभूमि पर्यावरण is modulated by climatological चक्र और पैटर्न such as the Madden-Julian oscillation, El niño-southern दोलन, and the अटलांटिक multidecadal oscillation.
Others form जब अन्य प्रकार of cyclones acquire तीव्र characteristics.
तीव्र systems हैं तब स्थानांतरित by परिचालन हवाएँ in the क्षोभमण्डल ; if the शर्तें remain अनुकूल, the tropical disturbance intensifies, and can भी develop an eye.
on the अन्य समाप्त of the वर्णक्रम, if the शर्तें around the प्रणाली deteriorate or the tropical cyclone makes landfall, the प्रणाली weakens and आखिरकार dissipates.
it is नहीं possible to artificially induce the dissipation of these systems साथ current प्रौद्योगिकी.
किर्क Douglas ( born Issur Danielovitch, ; दिसम्बर 9, 1916 ) is an अमरीकी स्टेज और फिल्मी actor, film निर्माता और author.

He is no.17 on the American Film Institute 's सूची of the महानतम male अमरीकी स्क्रीन legends of सब समय, बनाना उसे the highest-ranked जीना person on the list.
In 1996, he received the Academy Honorary Award `` for 50 सालो as a creative and moral force in the गति picture जातियाँ. ''
he is one of the last surviving actors इससे Hollywood 's `` सुनहरी आयु ''.
Robert क्लार्क `` bob '' Seger ( born may 6, 1945 ) is an American चट्टान और roll singer-songwriter, guitarist and pianist.
as a locally कामयाब detroit-area कलाकार, he performed and अंकित as Bob Seger and the Last सुना और bob seger System throughout the 1960s.

In 1973, he put साथ The Silver गोली Band, a group of Detroit-area संगीतकारों, साथ जिसको he became most कामयाब on the national level with the एल्बम सजीव गोली, recorded सजीव साथ the Silver गोली बैंड in 1975 at cobo हॉल in डेट्रॉयट, मिशिगन.
In 1976, he achieved a नेशनल breakout साथ the स्टुडियो एल्बम रात्रि चालें.
On उसके स्टुडियो albums, he also worked extensively with the alabama-based Muscle Shoals Rhythm Section, जिससे appeared on several of seger 's best-selling singles and albums.
a roots rocker with a क्लासिक raspy, shouting आवाज़, seger लिखा और अंकित गीतों कि dealt साथ प्रेम, women, blue-collar विषयवस्तु and थी an exemplar of heartland चट्टान.
Seger has अंकित अनेक hits, सहित `` Night Moves, '' `` Turn the Page, '' `` We 've मिला tonight, '' `` विरूद्ध the हवा, '' और shakedown that थी written लिये बेवर्ली पहाड़ियाँ Cop II और `` Like a चट्टान, '' और also co-wrote the ईगल्स ' number-one hit `` heartache tonight. ''
उसके iconic recording of `` Old Time चट्टान and Roll `` थी नामित एक of the Songs of the सदी in 2001.

Richard Milhous Nixon ( January 9, 1913 – April 22, 1994 ) was the 37th President of the संयुक्त States, serving from 1969 to 1974, when he became the only अध्यक्ष to resign the दफ्तर.
निक्सन था previously परोसा as a Republican u.S. representative and सीनेटर from कैलिफ़ोर्निया और as the 36th Vice अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States इससे 1953 to 1961.
निक्सन थी born in yorba लिंडा, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
He ग्रैजुएट इससे whittier कॉलेज in 1934 और Duke विश्वविद्यालयों स्कूल of विधि in 1937, returning to California to अभ्यास law.
He और उसके बीवी, पैट Nixon, moved to वॉशिंगटन to कार्य लिये the federal government in 1942.
he subsequently परोसा in the United States नेवी during World युद्ध ii.
निक्सन was निर्वाचित in कैलिफ़ोर्निया to the House of प्रतिनिधि in 1946 और to the Senate in 1950.
उसके pursuit of the alger Hiss case स्थापित his reputation as a leading anti-communist, और elevated उसे to नेशनल prominence.
He थी the running mate of ड्वाइट D. आइज़नहावर, the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी presidential nominee in the 1952 election.
Nixon served for आठ सालो as वाइस president.
he waged an unsuccessful अध्यक्षीय campaign in 1960, narrowly losing to जॉन F. कैनेडी, and खोया a रेस लिये राज्यपाल of California in 1962.
in 1968, he ran again लिये the presidency और थी निर्वाचित.
हालांकि Nixon initially escalated America 's involvement in the Vietnam War, he subsequently ended u.S. भागीदारी in 1973.
निक्सन 's visit to the People 's Republic of China in 1972 खोली diplomatic संबंध between the दो nations, and he initiated détente and the anti-ballistic मिसाइल Treaty with the Soviet संघ the same year.
domestically, उसके प्रशासन generally embraced policies कि transferred power इससे Washington to the states.
Among अन्य things, he शुभारम्भ initiatives to लड़ो cancer और illegal दवाएँ, imposed मजदूरी और price नियंत्रण, enforced desegregation of कुछ दक्षिणी schools, और established the पर्यावरणीय Protection एजेंसी.
हालांकि he presided over the चंद्र landings शुरूआत साथ अपोलो 11, he scaled वापस manned स्पेस खोजी.
he was re-elected by a भूस्खलन in 1972.
निक्सन 's second पद saw an अरब आयल embargo, the resignation of उसके vice अध्यक्ष, spiro agnew, और a continuing श्रेणी of खुलासे about the वाटरगेट कांड and अन्य misconduct by सदस्यों of the प्रशासन.
the scandal escalated, costing Nixon much of his राजनैतिक support, and on August 9, 1974, he resigned in the फेस of लगभग certain महाभियोग और हटाना from office.
बाद his इस्तीफा, he controversially received a pardon जारी by उसके successor, Gerald Ford.
in रिटायरमेंट, निक्सन 's कार्य as an elder statesman, authoring several books and undertaking अनेक विदेशी trips, helped to rehabilitate his पब्लिक चित्र.
He suffered a debilitating stroke on अप्रैल 18, 1994, और died four दिनों later at the आयु of 81.

The डोमिनिकन गणतंत्र annexation सन्धि caused कड़वा contention between अध्यक्ष Grant और sen. Sumner.
ब्रैडी 1869 ] ]
sen. sumner, opposed to अमरीकी imperialism in the Caribbean और fearful that annexation would lead to the conquest of the neighboring ब्लैक republic of हैती, became कायल कि भ्रष्टाचार lay पीछे the सन्धि, और कि मेन close to the अध्यक्ष साझा in the भ्रष्टाचार.
As अध्यक्ष of the Senate Foreign संबंध Committee, sen. sumner initially withheld his राय on the treaty on जनवरी 18, 1870.
sen. Sumner था महरूम लीक सूचना इससे सहायक Secretary of राज्य, bancroft डेविस, कि u.s. नवल जहाजों were being प्रयुक्त to protect President báez.
Sen. sumner 's कमेटी voted विरूद्ध annexation और at Sen. Sumner’s suggestion and काफी संभवतः to सहेजें the party इससे an भद्दा fight or the अध्यक्ष इससे शर्मिंदगी, the Senate आयोजित इसके बहस of the treaty पीछे closed doors in कार्यपालिका सत्र.
President ग्रान्ट persisted और भेजा messages to कॉंग्रेस in favor of annexation on March 14, 1870, और may 31, 1870.
in बंद सत्र, Sen. Sumner spoke out against the सन्धि ; warnng कि वहीँ would be परेशानी साथ the foreign nationals, noting the दीर्घकालिक विद्रोह कि took place on the द्वीप, और the रिस्क that the स्वतंत्रता of Haiti, पहचाना by the United States in 1862, would be खोया.
sumner stated कि ग्रान्ट 's use of the u.S. Navy as a protectorate थी a उल्लंघन of International विधि और असंवैधानिक.
Finally, on June 30, 1870 the treaty थी voted on by the सीनेट और विफल to gain the जरूरी 2/3 majority लिये treaty passage.
The following दिन, अध्यक्ष ग्रान्ट, अहसास betrayed by Sen. sumner, retaliated by ordering the dismissal of sumner’s close dost J. lothrop motley, दूत to ब्रिटेन.
by पतझड़, Sumner 's personal hostility to the अध्यक्ष थी पब्लिक knowledge, और he blamed the Secretary of State लिये failing to have resigned, rather than let ग्रान्ट have उसके way.
the two मेन, friends जबतक then, cooled into कड़वा दुश्मनों.
In दिसम्बर, 1870, स्टिल fearful कि ग्रान्ट meant to acquire Santo डोमिंगो somehow, sumner दिया a fiercely critical वाक accusing the अध्यक्ष of usurpation and Babcock of unethical conduct.
Already, President ग्रान्ट, समर्थित by his सचिव of राज्य हैमिल्टन मछली, था initiated a अभियान to depose sumner from the chairmanship of the सीनेट विदेशी संबंध Committee.
हालांकि sumner stated he was an `` प्रशासन man '', in addition to having stopped ग्रान्ट 's डोमिनिकन गणतंत्र सन्धि attempt, sumner था पराजित ग्रान्ट 's पूरा repeal of the कार्यकाल of दफ्तर Act, blocked Grant 's नामांकन of सिकंदर स्टीवर्ट to U.S. सचिव of Treasury, और महरूम a constant harassing फ़ोर्स pushing Reconstruction नीतियों तेज़ than ग्रान्ट had been willing to go.
ग्रान्ट resented Sumner 's बड़प्पन of manner, as खूब.
बताई once that sumner किया not believe in the बाइबल, the अध्यक्ष is supposed to have कहा that he थी नहीं चकित : `` he किया n't लिखें it. ''
as the दरार between Grant और sumner increased, sumner’s स्वास्थ्य began to decline.
जब the 42nd U.S. कॉंग्रेस convened on कूच 4, 1871, Senators संबद्ध साथ President Grant, known as ‘’new Radicals’’ voted to oust Sen. sumner इससे the सीनेट Foreign संबंध कमेटी chairmanship.
कारोबार आचार ( भी कॉरपोरेट ethics ) is a रूप of लागू ethics or professional ethics कि examines नैतिक सिद्धान्त और moral or ethical problems कि arise in a कारोबार environment.
it applies to सब aspects of business conduct and is प्रासंगिक to the conduct of individuals और संपूर्ण organizations.
Business आचार has दोनो normative and वर्णनात्मक dimensions.
as a corporate अभ्यास और a करियर specialization, the field is primarily normative.
Academics attempting to understand business बर्ताव employ descriptive विधि.
the दायरा and मात्रा of कारोबार नैतिक issues reflects the interaction of profit-maximizing बर्ताव साथ non-economic चिंताएं.
ब्याज in business आचार accelerated dramatically during the 1980s and 1990s, both भीतर प्रमुख corporations and within academia.
लिये उदाहरण, today most प्रमुख corporations promote उनके प्रतिबद्धता to non-economic values अंतर्गत headings ऐसे as आचार कोड और सोशल जिम्मेदारी charters.
आदम स्मिथ said, `` लोगों of the same trade seldom मिलें साथ, even लिये merriment और diversion, लकिन the वार्तालाप ends in a conspiracy विरूद्ध the public, or in some contrivance to उठाएँ prices. ''
Governments उपयोग कानून और regulations to पाइंट कारोबार बर्ताव in कया वे perceive to be फायदेमंद दिशानिर्देश.
Ethics implicitly regulates क्षेत्रों and विवरण of behavior कि झूठ परे सरकारी control.
The emergence of विशाल corporations with सीमित relationships और संवेदनशीलता to the communities in which वे operate accelerated the development of औपचारिक ethics regimes.
A बर्न is a type of चोट to flesh or स्किन caused by ऊष्मा, electricity, chemicals, घर्षण, or विकिरण.
Most burns affect only the superficial स्किन ( ज्ञात as सतही or पहला उपाधि ) or extend into the deeper स्किन but do not involve the पूरा मोटाई of the स्किन ( known as partial मोटाई or second degree ).
Rarely सब परतों of the स्किन or deeper tissues, such as muscle or अस्थि can be घायल in जिससे मामला the burn is either full thickness ( तीसरा उपाधि ) or चौथी उपाधि.
the treatment जरूरी depends on the गंभीरता of the burn.
Superficial burns maybe managed साथ little more than सरल पीड़ा killers जबकि major burns may आवश्यकता prolonged treatment in specialized बर्न centers.
कूलिंग साथ tap जल may सहायता पीड़ा और decrease क्षति however if exposure is prolonged it may result in कम body तापमान.
आंशिक मोटाई burns may आवश्यकता सफ़ाई with साबुन और जल followed by dressings.
फफोले चाहिए typically be बाएँ unbroken.
पूरा मोटाई burns प्रायः आवश्यकता सर्जिकल उपचार ऐसे as स्किन कलम और extensive burns often आवश्यकता विशाल राशि of intravenous fluids.
the सबसे आम जटिलताओं of burns हैं सम्बन्धित to संक्रमण.
जबकि विशाल burns can be fatal, आधुनिक treatments developed in the last 50 years have significantly improved the outcomes, विशेषकर in children and young वयस्कों.
globally परिचय 11 लाख people seek medical उपचार और 300,000 people die इससे burns.
in the संयुक्त राज्य, of those admitted to a बर्न बीच, लगभग 4 % die इससे उनके चोटों.
The long term outcome is primarily related to the आकार of बर्न and the आयु of the व्यक्ति effected.
The Atlantic Ocean, नहीं सहित आर्कटिक and Antarctic regions
This video थी taken by the क्रू of expedition 29 on फलक the ISS.
The pass starts इससे बस north-east of the द्वीप of न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड over the उत्तर Atlantic समंदर to central अफ़्रीकी, over दक्षिण Sudan.
The अटलांटिक समंदर is the second-largest of the world 's oceanic विभाजन.
साथ a कुल area of परिचय, it कवर लगभग 20 प्रतिशत of the Earth 's सतह and परिचय 29 percent of इसके जल surface क्षेत्रफल.
the पहला भाग of its नाम refers to एटलस of Greek mythology, making the अटलांटिक the `` समुद्र of Atlas ''.
the oldest ज्ञात mention of `` अटलांटिक '' is in The Histories of हिरोडोटस around 450 BC ( Hdt. 1.202.4 ) : Atlantis थलैसा ( यूनानी : ἀτλαντὶς θάλασσα ; अंग्रेज़ी : समुद्र of एटलस ).
the term ethiopic समंदर, निकला from इथियोपिया, was लागू to the southern अटलांटिक as लेट as the mid-19th सदी.
पहले europeans खोजा other oceans, the पद `` समंदर '' itself थी synonymous with the waters beyond the जलसन्धि of जिब्राल्टर कि we now know as the Atlantic.
the जल्दी यूनानियों believed this समंदर to be a gigantic river encircling the संसार.
the अटलांटिक समंदर occupies an elongated, s-shaped basin extending longitudinally between Eurasia and अफ़्रीकी to the ईस्ट, and the Americas to the वेस्ट.
as एक घटक of the interconnected global ocean, it is कनेक्ट in the north to the आर्कटिक Ocean ( जिससे is sometimes माना a sea of the अटलांटिक ), to the प्रशांत समंदर in the दक्षिणपश्चिम, the Indian समंदर in the southeast, और the Southern Ocean in the दक्षिण.
( अन्य definitions describe the Atlantic as extending southward to Antarctica. )
the equator subdivides it into the उत्तर Atlantic समंदर और दक्षिण अटलांटिक समंदर.
due to उनके long-term हठ, और the need लिये a unique identifier in issuing forecasts and warnings, tropical cyclones and subtropical cyclones हैं given names according to policy ( see Tropical cyclone नामकरण ).
The following हैं lists इससे जिससे ये तीव्र और उपोष्ण चक्रवात names हैं निकला.
White लाइट is dispersed by a prism into the रंगों of the optical spectrum.
the दृश्य वर्णक्रम is the portion of the इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक spectrum कि is visible to ( can be detected by ) the इंसान नजर.
Electromagnetic विकिरण in this range of wavelengths is called दृश्य light or बस light.
A ठेठ इंसान नजर होगा respond to wavelengths इससे परिचय 390 to 700 nm.
in terms of आवृत्ति, इस corresponds to a band in the vicinity of 430–790 THz.
a light-adapted नजर generally रै इसके अधिकतम संवेदनशीलता at around 555 nm ( 540 thz ), in the ग्रीन प्रदेश of the ऑप्टिकल वर्णक्रम ( देखिए : दीप्ति फलन ).
the वर्णक्रम does नहीं, however, contain सब the रंगों that the इंसान आँखें और brain can distinguish.
Unsaturated colors ऐसे as pink, or जामुनी विसंगतियाँ ऐसे as magenta, are absent, लिये उदाहरण, क्युकी वे can be made तभी by a mix of अनेक wavelengths.
रंगों containing तभी एक wavelength हैं also called pure रंगों.
Visible wavelengths pass through the `` ऑप्टिकल window ``, the प्रदेश of the इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक वर्णक्रम which allows wavelengths to pass largely unattenuated through the Earth 's माहौल.
An उदाहरण of this घटना is कि clean एयर scatters blue light अधिक than रेड wavelengths, और so the midday आसमान appears ब्लू.
the ऑप्टिकल खिड़की is also called the दृश्य खिड़की because it overlaps the human visible जवाब spectrum.
the निकट infrared ( NIR ) window झूठ बस out of the इंसान vision, as खूब as the Medium Wavelength ir ( mwir ) खिड़की और the long wavelength or दूर इन्फ्रारेड ( LWIR or fir ) window हालांकि other पशु may अनुभव them.
अनेक species can see लाइट with बारंबारता outside the `` visible spectrum, '' which is पारिभाषित in शर्तें of human दृष्टि.
मधुमक्खियों और many other कीट can detect पराबैंगनी light, which helps उन्हें find मकरंद in पुष्प.
संयंत्र species that depend on कीट परागण may owe reproductive कामयाबी to उनके रूप in पराबैंगनी लाइट, बल्कि than how colorful वे appear to humans.
पक्षियों, too, can देखिए into the ultraviolet ( 300–400 nm ), and some have sex-dependent markings on उनके plumage कि हैं visible तभी in the ultraviolet range.
Many animals कि can देखिए into the पराबैंगनी दायरा, however, can not see red light or कोई अन्य reddish wavelengths.
मधुमक्खियों ' visible वर्णक्रम ends at परिचय 590nm, बस पहले the नारंगी wavelengths प्रारंभ.
पक्षियों, however, can see कुछ रेड wavelengths, लकिन नहीं as अनेक as humans.
zebras ( or ) हैं several प्रजाति of African equids ( horse family ) संयुक्त by their distinctive black and श्वेत धारियाँ.
Their धारियाँ आइये in अलग patterns, unique to each व्यक्तिगत.
वे हैं generally सोशल पशु कि सजीव in छोटी harems to large herds.
नापसंद उनके closest रिश्तेदारों, घोड़े और asses, zebras have never महरूम truly domesticated.
वहीँ हैं तीन species of zebras : the मैदान zebra, the Grévy 's zebra और the mountain जेब्रा.
the plains जेब्रा और the mountain zebra belong to the subgenus hippotigris, but grévy 's जेब्रा is the sole species of subgenus Dolichohippus.
The latter resembles an गधा, to जिससे it is closely related, जबकि the पूर्व दो are more horse-like.
सब तीन belong to the genus equus, along with other living equids.
The अद्वितीय धारियाँ of zebras मेक उन्हें एक of the animals सबसे परिचित to people.
वे occur in a variety of habitats, such as grasslands, savannas, woodlands, thorny scrublands, kyu, and coastal hills.
however, विभिन्न anthropogenic कारकों have had a severe impact on zebra populations, in particular hunting लिये खालें and habitat विनाश.
grévy 's जेब्रा and the mountain zebra हैं endangered.
While मैदान zebras हैं much अधिक plentiful, एक subspecies, the quagga, became विलुप्त in the लेट 19th century – though वहीँ is currently a plan, पुकारा the quagga Project, कि aims to breed zebras that are phenotypically similar to the quagga in a प्रक्रम पुकारा breeding वापस.

a प्राकृतिक मेहराब produced by the erosion of differentially weathered चट्टान in Jebel kharaz, जॉर्डन
Erosion is the प्रक्रम by जिससे soil and rock हैं removed from the Earth 's सतह by exogenetic प्रक्रियाओं ऐसे as wind or जल प्रवाह, and then transported and deposited in other स्थितियाँ.
While अपरदन is a प्राकृतिक प्रक्रम, इंसान activities have increased by 10-40 times the rate at जिससे erosion is occurring globally.
excessive अपरदन causes समस्याएं such as मरुस्थलीकरण, decreases in agricultural उत्पादकता due to land degradation, sedimentation of जलमार्गों, और ecological पतन due to घाटा of the nutrient समृद्ध upper मृदा परतों.
जल और wind erosion हैं now the two primary कल्याणकारी of जमीन degradation ; संयुक्त, वे हैं जिम्मेदार लिये 84 % of degraded acreage, making excessive अपरदन एक of the सबसे significant वैश्विक पर्यावरणीय समस्याएं.
औद्योगिक कृषि, deforestation, roads, anthropogenic जलवायु बदलें और शहरी sprawl हैं amongst the सबसे significant human activities in लिहाज़ to उनके प्रभाव on stimulating अपरदन.
however, वहीँ हैं अनेक उपलब्धियाँ वैकल्पिक land उपयोग practices कि can काटना or सीमा अपरदन, such as terrace -building, no-till कृषि, और revegetation of denuded soils.

संयुक्त राज्य territory is कोई extent of प्रदेश अंतर्गत the jurisdiction of the federal सरकारी of the United States, including सब waters ( around islands or continental tracts ) और सब u.s. नवल vessels.
the संयुक्त राज्य has traditionally proclaimed the sovereign rights for exploring, exploiting, conserving, and मैनेजिंग its territory.
इस extent of territory is all the area belonging to, और अंतर्गत the डोमिनियन of, the संयुक्त States संघीय सरकारी ( which शामिल tracts lying at a distance इससे the देश ) लिये प्रशासनिक और अन्य purposes.
the United States कुल territory includes a उपसमुच्चय of राजनैतिक divisions.
The u.S. government is a government साथ delegated शक्तियां अंतर्गत the United States संविधान.
`` The powers नहीं प्रतिनिधित्व to the संयुक्त States by the संविधान, nor निषिद्ध by it to the States, are reserved to the राज्य क्रमशः, or to the लोगों '' by the दसवाँ amendment.

A cord of wood
the cord is a ईकाई of माप of शुष्क volume प्रयुक्त in कनाडा and the संयुक्त राज्य to measure ईधन and pulpwood.
A cord is the amount of wood कि, when `` क्रमित and खूब stowed '' ( arranged so pieces हैं लकीर, parallel, touching और कॉम्पैक्ट ), occupies a volume of.
This corresponds to a खूब stacked woodpile ऊँची, long, और deep ; or कोई अन्य arrangement of linear माप कि yields the वही volume.
the नाम cord probably comes इससे the उपयोग of a cord or स्ट्रिंग to measure it.

The संसार Trade Center is a जटिल of इमारतें अंतर्गत construction in Lower Manhattan, नई York नगर, संयुक्त States, replacing an earlier जटिल of सात इमारतें साथ the same नाम on the वही साईट.
the original World व्यापार बीच प्रदर्शित लैंडमार्क जुड़वा towers, जिससे खोली on अप्रैल 4, 1973 और were destroyed in the September 11 हमले of 2001, साथ साथ 7 संसार व्यापार बीच.
the अन्य buildings in the complex यहूद क्षतिग्रस्त in the हमले, और their तबाह यहूद eventually demolished.
The साईट is होने rebuilt साथ पाँच नई skyscrapers and a memorial to those मारे in the attacks.
, तभी one skyscraper रै महरूम समाप्त ; the अन्य चार हैं अपेक्षित to be completed पहले 2020.
एक World Trade बीच होगा be the सीसे भवन लिये the new जटिल, reaching more than 100 stories at इसके पूर्णता.
it became the tallest building in नई York City on April 30, 2012, और is expected to be finished by 2013.
a छठे मीनार is प्रतीक्षारत confirmation.
At the समय of उनके पूर्णता, the original 1 संसार व्यापार बीच ( the उत्तर Tower ) और 2 World व्यापार बीच ( the दक्षिण मीनार ), ज्ञात collectively as the `` Twin Towers '', were the tallest इमारतें in the world.
The अन्य buildings included 3 WTC ( the मैरियट संसार व्यापार बीच ), 4 wtc, 5 wtc, 6 wtc, and 7 wtc.
सब of ये इमारतें यहूद निर्मित between 1975 and 1985.
the लागत for the construction थी $ 400 million ( $ in डॉलर ).
the complex थी स्तिथ in the heart of New York नगर 's downtown financial district और contained 13.4 लाख वर्गाकार फीट ( 1.24 लाख m2 ) of दफ्तर स्पेस.
the World व्यापार Center अनुभवी a आग on, 1975, a bombing on, 1993 और a डकैती on, 1998.
In 1998, the बंदरगाहों प्राधिकार decided to privatize the World Trade Center, leasing the buildings to a निजी कम्पनी to मैनेज, और awarded the पट्टे to Silverstein Properties in.
on the morning of सितंबर 11, 2001, Al-Qaeda -संबद्धd hijackers flew two Boeing 767 jets into the complex, one into each मीनार, in a समन्वित terrorist आक्रमण.
बाद burning लिये 56 मिनट्स, the दक्षिण मीनार ( 2 ) collapsed, followed a half-hour बाद by the उत्तर मीनार ( 1 ), with the हमले on the संसार Trade Center resulting in 2,753 मौतों.
गिरना debris from the मीनारें, संयुक्त with fires कि the मलबा initiated in several surrounding इमारतें, led to the आंशिक or पूरा पतन of सब the अन्य buildings in the जटिल and caused अनर्थकारी क्षति to ten अन्य large structures in the surrounding क्षेत्रफल.
the process of cleanup और recovery at the World व्यापार Center site took आठ months.

Periodic table साथ इलेक्ट्रॉन शेल
an electron शेल may be विचार of as an कक्षा followed by electrons around an atom 's केंद्रक.
the closest shell to the nucleus is called the `` 1 shell '' ( also पुकारा `` K शेल '' ), followed by the `` 2 shell '' ( or `` l shell '' ), then the `` 3 शेल '' ( or `` m शेल '' ), and so on दूर और दूर इससे the केंद्रक.
The शेल अक्षर K, l, m,..., प्रयुक्त in the x-ray notation, हैं वर्णमाला.
Each शेल can contain only a fixed क्रमांक of electrons : The 1st शेल can hold up to दो electrons, the 2nd shell can थाम up to eight electrons, the 3rd शेल can थाम up to 18, and 4th shell can थाम up to 32 और so on.
Since electrons are electrically attracted to the nucleus, an atom 's electrons होगा generally occupy बाहरी shells only if the more भीतरी शेल have already been completely भर by other electrons.
however, this is not a strict requirement : अणु may have two or भी तीन incomplete बाहरी शेल.
( देखिए Madelung नियम for more विवरण. )
For an स्पष्टीकरण of why electrons exist in ये shells देखिए इलेक्ट्रॉन configuration.
the electrons in the outermost occupied shell ( or shells ) determine the chemical properties of the अणु ; it is पुकारा the valence शेल.
Each शेल consists of एक or more subshells, and प्रत्येक subshell consists of एक or more परमाणु orbitals.

Oil मंच Mittelplate in the उत्तर समुद्र
An oil platform, ( offshore मंच or colloquially oil रिग ) is a विशाल ढांचा with सुविधाएं to ड्रिल कुएं, to extract and प्रक्रम आयल and natural गैस, और to temporarily स्टोर product जबतक it can be brought to shore लिये शोधन and marketing.
in अनेक cases, the मंच contains सुविधाएं to हाउस the workforce as खूब.
depending on the हालातों, the मंच may be फिक्स्ड to the समंदर मंजिल, may consist of an कृत्रिम द्वीप, or may float.
रिमोट subsea wells may भी be connected to a platform by flow लाइनों and by umbilical connections.
These subsea solutions may consist of one or more subsea wells, or of one or more manifold केंद्रों लिये अनेक कुएं.

The White हाउस, the president 's आधिकारिक निवास and बीच of the प्रशासन
अंतर्गत the United States संविधान, the अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य is the सिर of राज्य और head of government of the संयुक्त राज्य.
as मुख्य of the executive branch और सिर of the संघीय सरकारी as a पूरे, the प्रेसिडेंसी is the highest राजनैतिक office in the संयुक्त States by influence और recognition.
The अध्यक्ष is भी the commander-in-chief of the संयुक्त राज्य Armed Forces.
The अध्यक्ष is indirectly निर्वाचित to a four-year पद by an Electoral कॉलेज ( or by the हाउस of Representatives चाहिए the चुनावी कॉलेज असफल to award an absolute बहुमत of मत to कोई व्यक्ति ).
Since the ratification of the twenty-second Amendment to the United राज्य Constitution in 1951, no व्यक्ति may be elected President अधिक than twice, और no एक who रै परोसा more than दो years of a term to जिससे किसी else थी elected may be elected अधिक than एकबार.
Upon the मौत, resignation, or removal इससे office of an incumbent अध्यक्ष, the वाइस अध्यक्ष assumes the दफ्तर.
the President जरूर be at तनिक 35 सालो of age और a `` natural born '' नागरिक of the संयुक्त राज्य.
इस list includes only those व्यक्तियों जो यहूद sworn into office as अध्यक्ष following the ratification of the United States Constitution, जिससे took प्रभाव on कूच 4, 1789.
For अमरीकी नेताओ before this ratification, see President of the Continental Congress.
the list does नहीं शामिल कोई एक्टिंग राष्ट्रपतियों under the twenty-fifth amendment to the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान.
There have been 43 लोगों sworn into दफ्तर, और 44 presidencies, as ग्रोवर क्लीवलैंड served two non-consecutive terms and is गिने क्रमबद्धता as दोनो the 22nd और 24th president.
Of the individuals निर्वाचित as अध्यक्ष, four died in दफ्तर of प्राकृतिक कल्याणकारी ( विलियम Henry Harrison, Zachary टेलर, वारेन G. हार्डिंग, और फ्रैंकलिन D. रूज़वेल्ट ), four यहूद assassinated ( अब्राहम Lincoln, James A. Garfield, William mckinley, और John F. Kennedy ) और एक resigned ( Richard निक्सन ).
जार्ज Washington, the पहला अध्यक्ष, थी उदघाटन in 1789 after a unanimous vote of the Electoral College.
William Henry हैरिसन spent the shortest time in दफ्तर with 32 days in 1841, और Franklin D. Roosevelt खर्च the longest साथ over बारह सालो, लकिन died shortly into उसके चौथी पद in 1945.
he is the तभी president to serve more than two terms, and a संवैधानिक amendment, affecting राष्ट्रपतियों बाद हैरी Truman, थी passed to सीमा the number of टाइम्स an individual can be elected अध्यक्ष.
Andrew जैक्सन, the सातवाँ president, थी the first to be elected by men of सब classes in 1828 बाद most laws barring non-land-owners from मतदान were repealed.
वारेन Harding थी the first elected after women gained voting अधिकारों in 1920.

जॉन F. Kennedy रै महरूम the तभी president of Roman Catholic आस्था, and the current president, Barack ओबामा, is the first president of African descent.

A suppressor, ध्वनि suppressor, or sound मॉडरेटर, is a यंत्र संलग्न to or part of the बैरल of a firearm which reduces the राशि of रव, और प्रायः the amount of muzzle flash, generated by firing the हथियार.
a suppressor can be used दोनो साथ a firearm and साथ संपीडित air गन.
Though it is sometimes referred to as a silencer, this पद is a misnomer popularized by cinematic fiction : the sound of a प्रक्षेप्य, especially एक चलती faster than the speed of ध्वनि, through the एयर can नहीं be eliminated.
using a suppressor in long distance शूटिंग ( i.e. वृहद than 300 meters ) can lessen, or retard, the report at the पल of प्रभाव, and create the छाप of खामोशी निकट the निशाना.
the रव सुना near the muzzle as a प्रक्षेप्य पत्ते the barrel, हालांकि subdued, is not silent at all.
a suppressor is प्रायः a मेटल बेलन साथ आतंरिक mechanisms to reduce the ध्वनि of firing by slowing the escaping propellant gas और sometimes by reducing the गति of the गोली.
Early suppressors were created around the शुरूआत of the 20th सदी by several आविष्कारक.
American inventor hiram Percy Maxim ( not to be उलझन साथ Hiram Stevens कहावत, hiram पर्सी 's पिता, and the inventor of the Maxim Machine गन ), is credited साथ inventing और selling the first commercially कामयाब models circa 1902 ( patented 30 कूच 1909 ).
कहावत gave उसके device the trademarked name कहावत Silencer.
the muffler लिये आतंरिक दहन इंजन was developed in parallel साथ the firearm suppressor by कहावत in the early 20th century, using अनेक of the वही तकनीकों to provide quieter-running engines ( in अनेक यूरोपीय देशों ऑटोमोबाइल mufflers are स्टिल पुकारा silencers ).
The word silencer in reference to गन suppressor remains in widespread use, हालांकि it रै चूंकि गिरे out of एहसान साथ कुछ, especially among the firearms उद्योग, होने replaced साथ the अधिक वस्तुतः accurate पद ध्वनि suppressor or बस suppressor, क्युकी a `` sound suppressor '' करता नहीं `` silence '' कोई हथियार, rather it eliminates muzzle फ्लैश and reduces the sonic दबाव of a firearm discharging.
Common usage और u.S. विधान language favor the historically पहले पद, silencer.
in u.S. law, the शर्तें `` firearm मफलर '' और `` firearm silencer '' हैं synonymous.
suppressors यहूद regularly used by agents of the संयुक्त States Office of रणनीतिक Services, जो favored the newly designed High मानक HDM.22 long Rifle पिस्टल during World युद्ध ii.

According to oss research मुख्य Stanley लोवेल, Donovan ( an बूढ़ा and विश्वसनीय dost of the अध्यक्ष ) was लहराया into the ओवल दफ्तर, where रूज़वेल्ट थी dictating a अक्षर.
जबकि रूज़वेल्ट समाप्त his message, Donovan turned his back and fired टेन गोलियाँ into a sandbag he had brought साथ him, announced कया he था किया और हात the धूम्रपान gun to the astonished president.

In the संयुक्त States, a homeowner association is a corporation formed by a real एस्टेट developer लिये the purpose of विपणन, managing, और selling of homes and लोट in a आवासीय subdivision.

There हैं अनेक breeds of गिनी pig जिससे have महरूम विकसित since इसके domestication ca. 5000 BC.
Breeds vary widely in रूप और purpose, ranging from show breeds with long, बहती hair to those in use as मॉडल organisms by विज्ञान.
From ca. 1200 ad to the स्पेनी conquest of the इन्का Empire in 1532, चयनात्मक प्रजनन by indigenous दक्षिण American peoples resulted in many varieties of घरेलू गिनी pigs, जिससे form the आधार लिये कुछ of the आधुनिक domestic breeds.

To this समाप्त, various प्रतिस्पर्धी breeding संगठन were founded by fanciers.

Similar organizations मौजूद in ऑस्ट्रेलिया ( Australian National cavy Council ) और नई जीलैंड ( नई जीलैंड cavy क्लबों ).

हालांकि there are many breeds of Guinea pig, only a few breeds are commonly मिला on the दिखाएँ तालिका as पालतु.

The छोटी hair, abyssinian, peruvian और sheltie ( aka Silkie ) breeds हैं those सबसे frequently देखी as पालतु, और the former तीन are the कोर breeds in the history of the competitive showing of गिनी सूअर.
in जोड to उनके मानक form, nearly सब breeds आइये in a Satin variant.

The ribosome assembles polymeric protein अणुओं जिनकी sequence is नियंत्रित by the अनुक्रम of messenger RNA molecules.
इस is जरूरी by सब living cells और associated viruses.
the राइबोसोम ( इससे ribonucleic एसिड and the यूनानी soma, अर्थ `` देह '' ) is a विशाल and complex आणविक यंत्र, found within सब जीना cells, that serves as the प्राथमिक site of biological प्रोटीन संश्लेषण ( अनुवाद ).
ribosomes कड़ी amino acids together in the order निर्दिष्ट by messenger RNA ( mrna ) अणुओं.
Ribosomes consist of two major subunits—the छोटी ribosomal subunit reads the mrna, जबकि the large subunit joins अमीनो acids to form a polypeptide chain.
Each subunit is रचित of एक or अधिक ribosomal rna ( rRNA ) molecules और a किस्में of प्रोटीन.
The अनुक्रम of DNA encoding लिये a protein may be कॉपी अनेक times into messenger RNA ( mRNA ) जंजीरों of a समान अनुक्रम.
ribosomes can bind to an mrna chain and उपयोग it as a टेम्पलेट for determining the सही अनुक्रम of amino acids in a particular protein.
अमीनो acids हैं selected, एकत्रित और carried to the ribosome by ट्रांसफ़र rna ( tRNA अणुओं ), जिससे डालें one part of the राइबोसोम और bind to the मेसेंजर RNA कड़ी.
The संलग्न अमीनो acids are तब linked together by another भाग of the राइबोसोम.
एकबार the protein is produced, it can तब 'fold ' to उपज a विशिष्ट कार्यात्मक three-dimensional ढांचा.
A राइबोसोम is बना from देवालय of rnas और प्रोटीन और is इसलिए a ribonucleoprotein.
Each ribosome is विभाजित into दो subunits : the छोटी subunit बांधता to the mrna पैटर्न, while the larger subunit binds to the trna और the amino acids.
जब a राइबोसोम finishes reading an mrna molecule, ये दो subunits विभाजित apart.
ribosomes हैं ribozymes, क्युकी the catalytic peptidyl transferase कार्यकलाप कि links अमीनो acids साथ is performed by the ribosomal rna.
Ribosomes from bacteria, archaea और eukaryotes ( the three domains of जीवन on धरती ) differ in their size, अनुक्रम, ढांचा, और the अनुपात of प्रोटीन to rna.
the differences in structure allow कुछ एंटीबायोटिक to मार जीवाणु by inhibiting their ribosomes, जबकि leaving इंसान ribosomes unaffected.
in जीवाणु और आर्किया, अधिक than एक राइबोसोम may move साथ a सिंगल mrna कड़ी at एक time, each `` reading '' इसके अनुक्रम and producing a corresponding प्रोटीन molecule.
the ribosomes in the mitochondria of eukaryotic cells functionally resemble अनेक सुविधाएँ of those in bacteria, reflecting the संभावित विकासवादी origin of mitochondria.
अल्बर्ट क्लॉड, ईसाई de Duve, और जार्ज एमिल Palade were jointly awarded the नोबेल Prize in Physiology or आयुर्विज्ञान, in 1974, लिये the discovery of the ribosomes.
The Nobel पुरस्कार in रसायन 2009 was awarded to venkatraman रामकृष्णन, थामस A. steitz and एडीए E. yonath लिये determining the विस्तृत structure और यांत्रिकी of the राइबोसोम.

Overview of the calvin साईकिल और कार्बन fixation
the light-independent reactions of photosynthesis हैं रासायनिक प्रतिक्रियाएँ that बदलें कार्बन dioxide and अन्य यौगिकों into glucose.
These reactions occur in the stroma, the fluid-filled area of a chloroplast बाहर of the thylakoid झिल्लियों.
ये reactions लो the light-dependent reactions और perform further रासायनिक प्रक्रियाओं on उन्हें.
वहीँ हैं तीन phases to the light-independent प्रतिक्रियाएँ, collectively पुकारा the calvin cycle : carbon fixation, कटौती प्रतिक्रियाएँ, और ribulose 1,5-bisphosphate ( RuBP ) regeneration.
despite इसके name, इस प्रक्रम occurs तभी जब light is available.
Plants do नहीं carry आउट the calvin cycle by night.
They, instead, रिलीज sucrose into the फ्लोएम इससे उनके starch reserves.
This प्रक्रम happens जब लाइट is उपलब्धियाँ स्वतंत्र of the दयालु of photosynthesis ( C3 carbon fixation, c4 कार्बन fixation, and crassulacean एसिड Metabolism ) ; CAM plants स्टोर malic एसिड in their vacuoles every night and रिलीज it by दिन in order to मेक this process work.
In mathematics, a वर्गाकार number or पूर्ण square is an पूर्णांक कि is the वर्गाकार of an integer ; in अन्य words, it is the product of some पूर्णांक साथ itself.
लिये example, 9 is a वर्गाकार क्रमांक, चूंकि it can be लिखा as.
The usual संकेतन for the सूत्र लिये the वर्गाकार of a क्रमांक is not the उत्पाद, लकिन the equivalent घातांक, प्रायः सुनाया as `` वर्गाकार ''.
the name वर्गाकार number comes इससे the नाम of the आकार ; see below.
वर्गाकार संख्याएँ हैं non-negative.
another रास्ता of saying कि a ( non-negative ) number is a वर्गाकार क्रमांक, is कि इसके square roots हैं again integers.
लिये उदाहरण, = ±3, so 9 is a वर्गाकार number.
a धनात्मक पूर्णांक कि has no पूर्ण वर्गाकार divisors मगर 1 is पुकारा square-free.
लिये a non-negative पूर्णांक, the th square number is, साथ being the zeroth square.
the अवधारणा of square can be विस्तारित to कुछ other number प्रणालियों.
if rational संख्याएँ are included, तब a वर्गाकार is the अनुपात of दो square integers, और, conversely, the अनुपात of two वर्गाकार integers is a square ( e.g., 4/9 = ( 2/3 ) 2 ).
starting with 1, वहीँ are वर्गाकार संख्याएँ up to और सहित, जहाँ the expression represents the मंजिल of the number.
the era of Good Feelings चिह्नित a काल in the राजनैतिक history of the संयुक्त States कि reflected a भाव of नेशनल purpose and a ख्वाहिश लिये unity among अमेरिकी in the aftermath of the Napoleonic युद्धों.
the era देखी the collapse of the federalist Party और an समाप्त to the bitter partisan विवादों between it and the प्रबल Democratic-Republican पार्टी दौरान the पहला पार्टी प्रणाली.
President जेम्स मुनरो endeavored to downplay दलगत संबद्ध in बनाना उसके nominations, with the परम goal of नेशनल unity और eliminating parties altogether from national राजनीती.
The काल is so closely संबद्ध with मुनरो 's presidency ( 1817–1825 ) और his प्रशासनिक goals that his नाम और the era हैं virtually synonymous.
The Era of Good Feelings चिह्नित a transition in अमरीकी राजनीती साथ the समाप्त of the Federalist पार्टी as अमेरिका began to develop after the War of 1812.
While अमेरिका थी experiencing growth और prosperity बाद the युद्ध with ब्रिटेन, इस era also marks the पहला उदाहरण of economic परेशानियों in the growing संयुक्त राज्य.
mirroring the अमरीकी System प्रस्तावित by हेनरी Clay, protective tariffs और the chartering of the Second बैंको of the United States जटिल the tension between the North and दक्षिण साथ the coming of the first financial crisis.
जबकि the term “era of Good Feelings” is प्रायः viewed साथ विडंबना because of the political turmoil, आर्थिक कारकों caused animosity between the North and South.
the नामांकन of the काल by इतिहासकारों as एक of “good feelings” is often conveyed with विडंबना or skepticism, as the इतिहास of the era थी एक in जिससे the राजनैतिक atmosphere was strained और divisive, especially among गिरोहों within the Monroe administration और the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी.
the phrase “Era of शुभ Feelings” थी coined by Benjamin रसेल, in the Boston Federalist newspaper, Columbian Centinel, on July 12, 1817, following Monroe 's विज़िट to बोस्टन, मैसाचुसेट्स as भाग of उसके good होगा दौरे of अमेरिका.

to शुरू with, the religious beliefs, practices, और identities of ईस्ट एशियाइ ( जो comprise the बहुमत of the world 's बौद्धों by कोई measure ) often मिश्रण buddhism साथ other traditions सहित Confucianism, the चाइनीज लोक religion, daoism, Shinto, और कोरियाई shamanism.

an अतिरिक्त चुनौती is the hostility of several national सरकारें ( often कम्युनिस्ट ones ऐसे as China or North कोरियाई ) to religion generally or to Buddhism specifically.
सरकारी नीतियों in ये देशों may encourage the under-reporting or non-reporting of धार्मिक adherence, resulting in आधिकारिक totals कि may drastically underestimate the क्रमांक of धार्मिक practitioners in ये देशों.

James Butler hickok ( may 27, 1837 – August 2, 1876 ), बेहतर ज्ञात as जंगली विधेयक hickok, थी a लोक नायिका of the अमरीकी Old West.

a मंगल रोवर is an स्वचालित मोटर vehicle जिससे propels itself आरपार the सतह of the ग्रह Mars after लैंडिंग.

There have been four successful robotically संचालित Mars rovers.

a financial ऑडिट, or अधिक accurately, an ऑडिट of financial statements, is the verification of the वित्तीय statements of a विधिक एंटिटी, with a दृश्य to express an ऑडिट opinion.
the ऑडिट opinion is intended to provide reasonable परख, लकिन नहीं निरपेक्ष परख, that the financial statements are प्रस्तुत fairly, in सब सामग्री respects, and/or दे a true और fair दृश्य in accordance with the वित्तीय रिपोर्टिंग फ्रेमवर्क.
the purpose of an audit is provide और उद्देश्य स्वतंत्र examination of the वित्तीय कथन, जिससे increases the value और credibility of the financial कथन उत्पादित by प्रबन्धन, thus बढ़ाएँ उपयोक्ता विश्वास in the वित्तीय बयान, reduce investor risk और consequently reduce the cost of पूंजी of the preparer of the वित्तीय कथन.
वित्तीय audits हैं typically performed by firms of practicing accountants who हैं experts in वित्तीय रिपोर्टिंग.
The वित्तीय ऑडिट is one of अनेक assurance functions provided by हिसाब firms.
अनेक organizations separately employ or hire आतंरिक auditors, जो do नहीं attest to financial रिपोर्ट्स लकिन focus mainly on the आतंरिक नियंत्रण of the organization.
बाह्य auditors may चुनें to प्लेस सीमित रिलायंस on the कार्य of आतंरिक auditors.
Auditing promotes पारदर्शिता और accuracy in the financial disclosures बना by an संगठन, therefore would likely to reduce of ऐसे corporations to छिपाते unscrupulous dealings.
Internationally, the अंतरराष्ट्रीय मानकों on auditing ( isa ) जारी by the अंतरराष्ट्रीय auditing and Assurance Standards फलक ( iaasb ) is माना as the benchmark लिये ऑडिट process.
Almost all jurisdictions आवश्यकता auditors to follow the isa or a लोकल विभिन्नता of the isa.

the term चांदी dollar is प्रायः प्रयुक्त लिये कोई विशाल white metal सिक्का जारी by the United राज्य साथ a face value of एक डालर, हालांकि purists insist that a dollar is नहीं silver जबतक it contains कुछ of कि metal.
चांदी डॉलर, the पहला dollar coin issue, यहूद minted beginning in 1794.

The steeper the बैंको, the वृहद the g-forces.
This top-fuel dragster can accelerate इससे zero to in 0.86 सेकेंड.
This is a horizontal acceleration of 5.3 g. Combined साथ the लंबवत g-force in the stationary case the pythagorean theorem yields a g फ़ोर्स of 5.4 g.
g-force ( साथ g इससे गुरुत्वाकर्षक ) is a term लिये accelerations लगा as weight और measurable by accelerometers.
it is not a फ़ोर्स, प्रति se, but a फ़ोर्स प्रति ईकाई द्रव्यमान.
Since ऐसे a फ़ोर्स is perceived as a weight, कोई g-force can be वर्णित as a `` वज़न per unit mass '' ( देखिए the पर्याय specific weight ).
the g-force त्वरण अधिनियमों as a गुणक of weight-like शक्तियां लिये प्रत्येक ईकाई of an ऑब्जेक्ट 's mass, और ( सहेजें लिये certain इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक force influences ) is the कारण of an ऑब्जेक्ट 's acceleration in relation to free-fall.
इस त्वरण अनुभवी by an ऑब्जेक्ट is due to the vector sum of non-gravitational forces एक्टिंग on an ऑब्जेक्ट फ़्री to move.
The accelerations that हैं नहीं उत्पादित by गम्भीरता are termed proper accelerations, and it is तभी ये that हैं measured in g-force units.
वे कारण stresses and strains on वस्तुएँ.
क्युकी of these strains, large g-forces may be destructive.
gravitation एक्टिंग अलोन करता नहीं produce a g-force, भी हालांकि g-forces are expressed in multiples of the acceleration of a standard गम्भीरता.
यूँ, the standard गुरुत्वाकर्षक त्वरण at the Earth 's surface produces g-force तभी indirectly, as a result of resistance to it by mechanical शक्तियां.
The 1 g-force on an ऑब्जेक्ट बैठे on the धरती 's surface is caused by mechanical फ़ोर्स exerted in the upward direction by the मैदान, keeping the ऑब्जेक्ट from going into free-fall.
the upward फ़ोर्स from the मैदान ensures कि an ऑब्जेक्ट at rest on the धरती 's सतह is accelerating relative to the free-fall कंडीशन, जिससे is the path कि the object would follow जब गिरना freely toward the धरती 's center.
वस्तुएँ अनुमत to free-fall in an inertial trajectory under the influence of gravitation-only, महसूस no g-force.
इस is demonstrated by the `` zero-g '' शर्तें inside a freely falling लिफ्ट गिरना toward the धरती 's center ( in वैक्यूम ), or ( to शुभ approximation ) शर्तें inside a spacecraft in Earth orbit.
ये are उदाहरण of निर्देशांक त्वरण ( a बदलें in गति ) बगैर a सनसनी of वज़न.
the अनुभव of no g-force ( zero-g ), however it is produced, is synonymous with weightlessness.
In the absence of गुरुत्वाकर्षक fields, or in directions at right angles to them, proper और निर्देशांक accelerations हैं the same, and any coordinate acceleration जरूर be produced by a सम्बन्धित g-force acceleration.
an उदाहरण here is a प्रक्षेपास्त्र in free space, in जिससे simple changes in गति हैं produced by the इंजन, और produce g-forces on the प्रक्षेपास्त्र and passengers.

the augur थी a पुजारी और official in the शास्त्रीय संसार, विशेषकर ancient Rome and etruria.
उसके प्रमुख भूमिका थी to interpret the will of the देवताओं by अध्ययन the उड़ान of birds : whether they हैं उड़ती in groups or अलोन, कया noises वे make as they fly, दिशा of flight और कया kind of पक्षियों they are.
This was known as `` लेने the auspices. ''
the रस्म और फलन of the augur थी central to कोई major undertaking in रोमन society—public or private—including matters of युद्ध, commerce, और धर्म.
the रोमन इतिहासकार Livy तनावों the importance of the augurs : `` Who करता not जान कि इस city was founded only after लेने the auspices, कि everything in युद्ध and in सलाम, at घर और विदेश, थी किया तभी बाद लेने the auspices ? ''
farmington पहाड़ियाँ is an affluent community in southeastern Michigan.
It is the दूसरी largest नगर in Oakland काउंटी in the u.S. state of मिशिगन.
Its जनसांख्यिकी थी 79,740 at the 2010 जनसांख्यिकी.
It is part of the upscale northwestern suburbs of Metropolitan डेट्रॉयट और is भी पूर्वोत्तर of शहर ऐन Arbor.
farmington पहाड़ियाँ consistently ranks as एक of the safest शहरों in the संयुक्त राज्य, as खूब as in the राज्य of मिशिगन.
in 2010, the क्षेत्रफल ranked as the 30th safest नगर in अमेरिका.
हालांकि the two शहरों have separate सेवाएं और addresses, farmington और farmington पहाड़ियाँ हैं often विचार of as the वही community.
