A fire extinguisher, flame extinguisher, or बस an extinguisher, is an क्रियाशील fire सुरक्षा यंत्र प्रयुक्त to बुझा or कंट्रोल छोटी फ़ायर, often in emergency situations.
it is not intended for use on an out-of-control आग, ऐसे as one जिससे रै reached the छत, endangers the user ( i.e., no एस्केप रूट, smoke, विस्फोट जोखिम, इत्यादि. ), or वरना requires the विशेषज्ञता of a fire department.
Typically, a fire extinguisher consists of a hand-held cylindrical pressure पोत containing an एजेंट जिससे can be discharged to extinguish a fire.
In the United States, fire extinguishers, in सब इमारतें अन्य than houses, are generally जरूरी to be सर्विस and inspected by a आग सुरक्षा service कम्पनी at तनिक annually.
Some jurisdictions require अधिक बारंबार सेवा लिये fire extinguishers.
the servicer places a tag on the extinguisher to indicate the प्रकार of सेवा performed ( annual निरीक्षण, रिचार्ज, नई fire extinguisher ) और जब.
There हैं दो प्रमुख types of आग extinguishers : भंडारित दबाव and cartridge-operated.
in भंडारित दबाव इकाई, the expellant is stored in the same कक्ष as the firefighting agent itself.
Depending on the agent प्रयुक्त, different propellants are used.
साथ शुष्क रासायनिक extinguishers, nitrogen is typically used ; जल and झाग extinguishers typically उपयोग एयर.
भंडारित pressure आग extinguishers are the सबसे आम प्रकार.
cartridge-operated extinguishers contain the expellant gas in a पृथक कार्ट्रिज that is punctured prior to discharge, exposing the propellant to the extinguishing एजेंट.
This प्रकार is not as आम, used primarily in क्षेत्रों ऐसे as industrial facilities, जहाँ they receive higher-than-average use.
वे have the advantage of simple and संकेत recharge, allowing an operator to निर्वहन the extinguisher, रिचार्ज it, और return to the आग in a उचित राशि of समय.
Unlike भंडारित दबाव प्रकार, these extinguishers उपयोग संपीडित carbon dioxide instead of नाइट्रोजन, हालांकि नाइट्रोजन cartridges are used on low तापमान ( -60 rated ) मॉडल.
कार्ट्रिज संचालित extinguishers are available in dry रासायनिक और शुष्क powder types in the U.S. and in water, wetting एजेंट, झाग, dry रासायनिक ( वर्ग एबीसी और B.C. ), और dry चूर्ण ( क्लास d ) प्रकार in the बाकी of the world.
आग extinguishers are further विभाजित into हैंडहेल्ड और cart-mounted, also पुकारा wheeled extinguishers.
Handheld extinguishers तौल from 0.5 to 14 kilograms ( 1 to 30 पाउंड ), और हैं hence, easily पोर्टेबल by हाथ.
cart-mounted इकाई typically तौल 23+ गामा ( 50+ पाउंड ).
ये wheeled मॉडल हैं सबसे commonly मिला at निर्माण sites, airport runways, heliports, as well as docks and marinas.
देशी Americans in the United States are the स्वदेशी peoples in उत्तर America भीतर the boundaries of the present-day महाद्वीपीय United राज्य, अलास्का, और the island राज्य of हवाई.
They हैं रचित of numerous, पृथक देशी अमरीकी जनजातियों and जातीय समूह, अनेक of which survive as बरकरार राजनैतिक communities.
the शर्तें प्रयुक्त to refer to देशी अमेरिकी have महरूम विवादास्पद.
according to a 1995 U.S. Census census_bureau Bureau Census_Bureau set of घर interviews, सबसे of the respondents साथ an expressed वरीयता refer to themselves as अमरीकी इंडियंस ( or बस इंडियंस ), and this पद रै been अपनाया by प्रमुख अखबारों और कुछ अकादमिक समूह ; however, इस पद does not typically शामिल देशी Hawaiians or निश्चित अलास्कन natives, such as aleut, yup'ik, or इनुइट peoples.
चूंकि the समाप्त of the 15th सदी, the migration of europeans to the Americas, और उनके importation of africans as स्लेव, has led to centuries of conflict और adjustment between Old and नई World समाजों.
Europeans निर्मित most of the early लिखा ऐतिहासिक रिकार्ड परिचय देशी अमेरिकी after the colonists ' immigration to the americas.
Many Native Americans जिया as hunter-gatherer समाजों and told उनके histories by मौखिक परंपराओं.
in अनेक groups, महिलाओं carried आउट sophisticated cultivation of numerous किस्में of staple crops : मक्का, सेम और स्क्वैश.
the स्वदेशी cultures were quite अलग from those of the agrarian, proto-industrial, ज़्यादातर ईसाई immigrants इससे western यूरेशिया.
Many Native संस्कृतियों यहूद matrilineal ; the लोगों occupied lands लिये उपयोग of the entire जातियाँ, लिये शिकार or agriculture.
Europeans at that समय had patriarchal संस्कृतियों and had विकसित अवधारणाओं of individual प्रॉपर्टी अधिकारों with आदर to जमीन कि यहूद अत्यधिक अलग.
the मतभेद in संस्कृतियों between the स्थापित Native Americans and immigrant Europeans, as खूब as shifting alliances among different राष्ट्र of प्रत्येक संस्कृति through the सदियां, caused extensive राजनैतिक टेंशन, ethnic हिंसा और सोशल disruption.
The Native अमेरिकी suffered ऊँची fatalities इससे the contact साथ infectious Eurasian diseases, to which they था no acquired प्रतिरक्षण.
महामारी after European सम्पर्क caused the महानतम घाटा of जीवन for स्वदेशी populations.
estimates of the pre-Columbian जनसांख्यिकी of कया आज constitutes the u.S. vary significantly, ranging from 1 लाख to 18 लाख.
After the colonies revolted against Great ब्रिटेन और established the संयुक्त राज्य of America, अध्यक्ष George वॉशिंगटन और Henry नॉक्स conceived of the idea of `` civilizing '' Native Americans in preparation for सम्मिलन as U.S. नागरिकों.
सम्मिलन ( whether voluntary as with the Choctaw, or forced ) became a सतत नीति through अमरीकी administrations.
During the 19th century, the विचारधारा of manifest नियति became integral to the अमरीकी nationalist movement.
विस्तार of european-american populations to the वेस्ट बाद the अमरीकी क्रान्ति resulted in increasing दबाव on देशी अमरीकी lands, warfare between the समूह, and उठती तनाव.
in 1830, the u.S. कॉंग्रेस passed the Indian हटाना अधिनियम, authorizing the government to relocate देशी Americans from उनके homelands within established राज्य to lands west of the मिसिसिपी River, accommodating european-american expansion.
the first यूरोपीय अमेरिकी to एनकाउंटर the पश्चिमी आंतरिक जनजातियों were generally fur traders and trappers.
वहीँ यहूद भी जेसुइट प्रचारकों क्रियाशील in the उत्तरी टियर.
as United राज्य विस्तार reached into the American वेस्ट, settler और खनिक प्रवासियों आए into increasing विरोध with the ग्रेट Basin, ग्रेट Plains, and अन्य Western जनजातियों.
ये were complex nomadic cultures based on horse संस्कृति और seasonal बाइसन hunting.
वे carried आउट दमदार प्रतिरोध to संयुक्त राज्य incursions in the दशकों after the अमरीकी सिविल War, in a श्रेणी of भारतीय युद्धों, जिससे यहूद बारंबार up जबतक the 1890s, लकिन जारी into the 20th सदी.
The transcontinental railroad brought more non-natives into जनजातीय land in the west.
Over समय, the u.S. मजबूर a श्रेणी of treaties and जमीन cessions by the tribes, और स्थापित रिज़र्वेशन for them in many पश्चिमी states.
u.S. एजेंटों encouraged Native Americans to adopt European-style खेती और समान pursuits, but European-American agricultural technology of the time थी inadequate लिये प्रायः शुष्क रिज़र्वेशन lands.
In 1924, देशी Americans who यहूद नहीं already u.S. citizens were granted नागरिकता by Congress.
Contemporary Native Americans have a unique संबंध साथ the संयुक्त States क्युकी वे may be सदस्यों of nations, tribes, or bands with sovereignty and treaty अधिकारों.
सेंट्रल अमेरिका ( ) is the सेंट्रल geographic प्रदेश of the americas.
it is the southernmost, isthmian portion of the उत्तर अमरीकी महाद्वीप, which connects with South अमेरिका on the southeast.
When considered part of the एकीकृत महाद्वीपीय model, it is considered a उपमहाद्वीप.
Central अमेरिका consists of seven देशों : Belize, Costa रिका, el Salvador, ग्वाटेमाला, Honduras, निकारागुआ, and Panama.
सेंट्रल America is भाग of the mesoamerican biodiversity हॉटस्पॉट, जिससे extends इससे उत्तरी Guatemala through सेंट्रल Panama.
It is bordered by Mexico to the north, the caribbean समुद्र to the ईस्ट, the North प्रशांत Ocean to the वेस्ट, और Colombia to the south-east.
Central अमेरिका is an क्षेत्रफल of, or लगभग 0.1 % of the Earth 's surface.
as of 2009, its population थी estimated at 41,739,000.
it रै a घनत्व of 77 लोगों प्रति square kilometer.
scrubs is an American medical comedy-drama टेलीविज़न series निर्मित by विधेयक लॉरेंस कि aired from अक्तूबर 2, 2001 to कूच 17, 2010 on NBC और later एबीसी.

A steam इंजन is a ऊष्मा इंजन कि performs mechanical work using भाप as its working द्रव.
using boiling जल to उपज mechanical motion goes वापस परिचय 2,000 सालो, but जल्दी डिवाइस यहूद नहीं practical.
Since the लेट 1700s भाप इंजन have become a प्रमुख source of mechanical शक्ति.
The पहला applications यहूद निकालना water इससे mines.
in 1781 जेम्स Watt patented a steam engine कि produced continuous rotative motion.
These 10 hp engines सक्रिय a चौड़ी दायरा of निर्माण machinery to be powered.
the engines could be sited anywhere कि जल और coal or लकडी fuel could be प्राप्त.
by 1883, इंजन कि could provide 10,000 hp था become feasible.
Steam इंजन could भी be लागू to वाहनों ऐसे as traction इंजन और the railway इंजनों which हैं commonly बस पुकारा भाप इंजन outside अमेरिका.
The stationary भाप engine थी a कुंजी घटक of the औद्योगिक Revolution, allowing factories to locate जहाँ water power was अनुपलब्ध.
आज steam turbines generate परिचय 90 % of the electric शक्ति in the संयुक्त राज्य using a किस्में of heat स्त्रोत.
Steam इंजन are बाह्य दहन engines, जहाँ the working द्रव is पृथक from the combustion उत्पाद.
non-combustion ऊष्मा sources ऐसे as solar शक्ति, नाभिकीय power or geothermal energy may be used.
the ideal ऊष्मागतिक साईकिल used to analyze इस process is called the rankine साईकिल.
In the साईकिल, जल is heated into भाप in a बॉयलर जबतक it reaches a ऊँची दबाव.
जब विस्तारित through पिस्टन्स or turbines, mechanical work is done.
the reduced-pressure भाप is तब सघन and pumped वापस into the boiler.
In general उपयोग, the पद steam इंजन can refer to either the integrated भाप पौधे ( including बायलरों इत्यादि. ) such as रेल steam locomotives और portable engines, or may refer to the piston or टर्बाइन machinery alone, as in the beam engine and stationary भाप engine.
Specialized डिवाइस ऐसे as steam hammers और steam pile drivers are dependent on भाप supplied from a पृथक boiler.

एलिज़ाबेथ II ( एलिज़ाबेथ एलेक्जेंड्रा मरियम ; born 21 अप्रैल 1926 ) is the संवैधानिक monarch of 16 sovereign राज्य, known as the राष्ट्रमंडल realms, and their territories and dependencies, और सिर of the 54-member राष्ट्रमंडल of राष्ट्र.
वो is परम् राज्यपाल of the Church of इंग्लैण्ड और, in कुछ of her realms, carries the शीर्षक of Defender of the आस्था as भाग of her पूरा शीर्षक.
on her accession on 6 फ़रवरी 1952, एलिज़ाबेथ became सिर of the Commonwealth and महारानी regnant of seven independent Commonwealth countries : the United किंगडम, कनाडा, Australia, नई Zealand, दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी, Pakistan और Ceylon.
From 1956 to 1992, the number of उसके realms varied as territories gained स्वतंत्रता और some realms became republics.
at present, in जोड to the first चार aforementioned countries, Elizabeth is Queen of Jamaica, बारबाडोस, the बहामा, हरा, पापुआ नई गिनी, the Solomon Islands, तुवालू, Saint लूसिया, संत Vincent और the grenadines, Belize, अण्टीगुआ और Barbuda and Saint Kitts and Nevis.
उसके शासनकाल of सालो is फिलहाल the second longest for a अंग्रेजों monarch ; तभी Queen Victoria रै reigned longer at over 63 years.
एलिज़ाबेथ was born in London और educated privately at home.
उसके पिता acceded to the सिंहासन as George vi in 1936 on the abdication of उसके brother एडवर्ड viii, इससे जिससे time वो थी the heir presumptive.
She began to undertake पब्लिक कर्तव्य दौरान the दूसरी World युद्ध, in जिससे वो served in the auxiliary territorial Service.
in 1947, वो शादीशुदा प्रिंस फिलिप, ड्यूक of एडिनबर्ग, with जिसको she रै चार children : चार्ल्स, Anne, Andrew, और एडवर्ड.
Her राजतिलक service took प्लेस in 1953 और was the first to be televised.
the Queen 's many ऐतिहासिक विज़िट और बैठक शामिल a राज्य विज़िट to the Republic of Ireland और reciprocal visits to और इससे the पोप.
The Queen has देखी major संवैधानिक changes in उसके realms, such as devolution in the संयुक्त किंगडम and the patriation of the Canadian संविधान.
टाइम्स of निजी significance have included the births और विवाह of उसके children, the births of her grandchildren, the प्रतिष्ठापन of the प्रिंस of वेल्स, और the celebration of माइलस्टोन ऐसे as her Silver, Golden, and डायमंड Jubilees in 1977, 2002, and 2012, respectively.
प्रमुख कार्यक्रम in the महारानी 's शासनकाल have included the Troubles in उत्तरी आयरलैंड, the Falklands युद्ध, युद्धों साथ इराकी और the युद्ध in Afghanistan.
वहीँ have been टाइम्स of personal विषाद लिये her which शामिल the मौत of her father at 56, the हत्या of Prince फिलिप 's uncle, रब माउंटबेटन, the विश्लेषण of उसके children 's विवाह in 1992 ( a year deemed उसके annus horribilis ), the मौत in 1997 of उसके former daughter-in-law, डायना, राजकुमारी of Wales, और the deaths of उसके माँ और सिस्टर in 2002.
the महारानी has occasionally faced कठोर दबायें आलोचना of the royal family और रिपब्लिकन sentiments, but support लिये the monarchy और उसके निजी popularity remain ऊँची.
Christianity is the largest religion listed by australians in the नेशनल जनसांख्यिकी.
in the 2011 जनसांख्यिकी, 61.1 % of Australians यहूद listed as ईसाई.
ऑस्ट्रेलिया रै no official state धर्म और the ऑस्ट्रेलियाई Constitution protects स्वतंत्रता of धर्म.
the उपस्थिति of Christianity in Australia began with the आगमन of the पहला Fleet of British convicts in 1788.
the धर्म grew to खाता for 96.1 % of the नेशनल जनसांख्यिकी at the time of the संघ of Australia in 1901.
the Anglican Church of ऑस्ट्रेलिया ( formerly known as the गिरिजाघर of England in Australia ) remained the largest denomination जबतक 1986, when it थी surpassed by the रोमन कैथोलिक Church in Australia.
post-war बहुसंस्कृतिवाद और a मनाही in धार्मिक observance among कुछ sections of the population have diversified the demographics of धर्म in ऑस्ट्रेलिया.
of the roughly 61 % identifying as ईसाई in 2011, the largest denominations were either रोमन कैथोलिक ( 25 % ) or anglican ( 17 % ), with the तीसरा largest denomination होने the 5 % affiliated with the uniting गिरिजाघर in ऑस्ट्रेलिया.
post-war immigration रै grown the numbers belonging to churches like the Greek Orthodox archdiocese of Australia and वहीँ are large और growing Pentecostal groups, such as सिडनी 's hillsong गिरिजाघर.
the त्यौहार of Easter and क्रिसमस are public holidays in Australia.
around a क्वार्टर of students attend church स्कूलों और ईसाई संगठनों are अग्रणी non-government प्रदाताओं of health और welfare सेवाएं through organisations like कैथोलिक Health Australia, anglicare, UnitingCare ऑस्ट्रेलिया, the Salvation फौज and st विंसेंट de Paul समाज.
Historically significant Australian Christians have शामिल रेव dr जॉन Dunmore लैंग, संत मरियम MacKillop, कैथरीन हेलेन spence, पादरी David unaipon, the Reverend John Flynn और Pastor सर डग Nicholls.
ऊँची profile contemporary ऑस्ट्रेलियाई ईसाइयों शामिल : Tim Costello Baptist minister और वर्तमान सीईओ of संसार दृष्टि Australia, फ़्रैंक ब्रेनन, Jesuit human अधिकारों lawyer, Cardinal George Pell, Catholic archbishop of Sydney, फिलिप aspinall the वर्तमान anglican Primate और Archbishop of ब्रिसबेन, केविन Rudd, पूर्व मजदूर प्रधान मंत्री, and टोनी एबॉट, leader लिये the संघीय Opposition Liberal Party.
चार्टर बनाना कॉलेजिएट स्कूल, जिससे became yale College, October 9, 1701
yale University is a निजी आइवी लीग शोध university located in New हेवन, Connecticut.
संस्थापित in 1701 in the उपनिवेश of कनेक्टिकट, the विश्वविद्यालयों is the third-oldest institution of उच्चतर शिक्षा in the संयुक्त राज्य.
Originally चार्टर्ड as the `` कॉलेजिएट School '', the संस्था traces इसके roots to 17th-century clergymen जो sought to establish a college to train पादरी और राजनैतिक नेताओ for the colony.
In 1718, the College थी renamed `` yale कॉलेज '' to honor a gift इससे Elihu yale, a governor of the अंग्रेजों East India कम्पनी.
in 1861, the ग्रैजुएट स्कूल of कला और Sciences became the पहला U.S. संस्था to award the PhD. yale became a founding सदस्य of the Association of अमरीकी Universities in 1900.
Yale College थी रूपांतरित, शुरूआत in the 1930s, through the स्थापना of residential colleges : 12 now exist and दो अधिक are planned.
Yale employs over 1,100 faculty to सिखा और advise परिचय 5,300 undergraduate and 6,100 graduate और professional विद्यार्थी.
Almost all tenured professors सिखा undergraduate courses, अधिक than 2,000 of which हैं offered annually.
the विश्वविद्यालयों 's एसेट शामिल an endowment valued at $ 19.4 अरब, the second-largest of कोई अकादमिक संस्था in the संसार.
yale 's प्रणाली of अधिक than two दर्जन पुस्तकालयों holds 12.5 लाख आयतन.
49 नोबेल laureates have महरूम संबद्ध with the विश्वविद्यालयों as विद्यार्थी, संकाय, और स्टाफ.
Yale has produced many notable alumni, सहित पाँच u.S. राष्ट्रपतियों, 19 U.S. परम् Court Justices, और अनेक विदेशी heads of state.
At the graduate level, Yale विधि School, Yale स्कूल of आर्ट, और Yale School of Drama are consistently ranked the top programs in उनके फ़ील्ड.
yale Law स्कूल is the most selective विधि school in the संयुक्त States.
yale students compete intercollegiately as the Yale bulldogs in the ncaa Division i आइवी League.
the oldest intercollegiate एथलेटिक इवेंट in the संयुक्त राज्य is the yale-harvard regatta.
artemisia tridentata ( `` big sagebrush '' or `` sagebrush '' ) is an aromatic shrub इससे the परिवार Asteraceae, जिससे grows in arid और semi-arid शर्तें, throughout a दायरा of ठंडा desert, स्तान, और पहाड़ habitats in the Intermountain वेस्ट of North अमेरिका.
The देशी name `` sagebrush '' is also used लिये अनेक सम्बन्धित members of the genus artemisia, ऐसे as California sagebrush ( artemisia californica ).
Big Sagebrush and अन्य artemisia species are the प्रबल plants आरपार विशाल portions of the ग्रेट जलाशय, covering some 422,000 square मील in 11 पश्चिमी u.S. & Canadian राज्य.
it is the state पुष्प of नेवाडा.
sagebrush provides खाना और habitat लिये a किस्में of species, such as sage grouse, pronghorn antelope, gray vireo, pygmy rabbit, और mule हिरण.
बिग sagebrush was used as an हर्बल आयुर्विज्ञान by देशी Americans throughout the intermountain वेस्ट of North america—especially लिये preventing संक्रमण in wounds, stopping आतंरिक bleeding, and treating headaches और colds.
chemically, the active औषधीय constituents शामिल camphor, terpenoids, और tannins.
अनेक प्रमुख खतरे exist to ऋषि ब्रश ecosystems, सहित इंसान settlements, परिवर्तन to agricultural land, पशुधन grazing, invasive संयंत्र species, wildfires, और जलवायु change.
Yahoo ! Mail is a फ़्री ईमेल सेवा offered by the अमरीकी ढूंढें इंजन कम्पनी Yahoo !
It was शुभारम्भ in 1997, and, according to comscore, Yahoo ! मेल is the third-largest web-based ईमेल सेवा साथ 281 लाख users as of December 2012.
Currently, याहू ! offers three versions of Yahoo ! मेल.
The traditional `` Yahoo ! मेल Classic '' continues the availability of the असली इंटरफ़ेस introduced in 1997.
a version introduced in 2005 included a नई अजाक्स interface, drag-and-drop सुविधाएँ, improved search कार्यक्षमता, keyboard शॉर्टकट, पता auto-complete, टैब्स, और other updated सुविधाएँ.
In अक्तूबर 2010, याहू ! released a beta संस्करण of याहू ! Mail, जिससे included improvements to the डिज़ाइन, प्रदर्शन, search कार्यक्षमता, and Facebook संयोजन.
in May 2011, बीटा परीक्षण लिये the नई version रोका, and it became the default interface for Yahoo ! Mail.
in जल्दी 2008, याहू ! began offering असीमित mail भंडार to इसके उपयोक्ता in जवाब to heated competition in the फ़्री web-mail market खण्ड.
on जून 27, 2009, याहू ! मेसेंजर थी एकीकृत with याहू ! मेल.
टकोमा (, ) is a mid-sized शहरी port नगर and the county सीट of Pierce काउंटी, Washington, United States.
The नगर is on वॉशिंगटन 's Puget Sound, दक्षिणपश्चिम of Seattle, पूर्वोत्तर of the राज्य पूंजी, Olympia, और उत्तरपश्चिम of माउंट Rainier National पार्क.
The जनसांख्यिकी थी 198,397, according to the 2010 census.
Tacoma is the second-largest नगर in the Puget ध्वनि area और the third largest in the राज्य.
Tacoma also serves as the बीच of business activity लिये the दक्षिण ध्वनि प्रदेश, जिससे has a population of around 1 million people.
टकोमा अपनाया इसके नाम बाद the आसपास माउंट rainier, originally पुकारा माउंट tahoma.
it is known as the `` नगर of Destiny '' because the क्षेत्रफल was चुनी to be the western टर्मिनस of the Northern Pacific रेलरोड in the लेट 19th सदी.
the निर्णय of the railroad was influenced by Tacoma 's neighboring deep-water हार्बर, शुरुआत खाड़ी.
by connecting the खाड़ी with the railroad टकोमा 's motto became `` When rails मिलें sails. ''
आज Commencement खाड़ी serves the Port of टकोमा, a center of अंतरराष्ट्रीय trade on the प्रशांत Coast and वॉशिंगटन राज्य 's largest port.
जैसे most सेंट्रल cities, Tacoma suffered a prolonged decline in the mid-20th century as a result of suburbanization और divestment.
Since the 1990s, developments in the शहर कोर include the विश्वविद्यालयों of Washington टकोमा ; टकोमा Link, the पहला आधुनिक इलेक्ट्रिक लाइट रेल सेवा in the राज्य ; the state 's highest density of आर्ट and history museums ; and a लौटी urban waterfront, the thea foss Waterway.
साथ a long history of blue-collar मजदूर politics — इससे the रेलरोड workers of the 19th century, to the longshoremen of the 20th सदी, to the मजदूर Ready workers of today — Tacoma रै long been known लिये its rough, किरकिरी चित्र.
a song परिचय Tacoma, `` thrice सब अमरीकी '', by American singer-songwriter और former resident neko मामला, describes it as `` a dusty बूढ़ा गहना in the South Puget Sound / where the कारखानों churn / and the timber 's all cut bas ''.
tacoma-pierce काउंटी has महरूम नामित एक of the most livable areas in the country.
टकोमा was भी recently listed as the 19th सबसे walkable नगर in the देश.
In कंट्रास्ट, the नगर is also क्रमित as the सबसे stressed-out नगर in the country in a 2004 सर्वेक्षण.
In 2006, women 's पत्रिका Self named टकोमा the `` सबसे sexually स्वस्थ City '' in the United States.
In 2012, the Advocate gave टकोमा the शीर्षक of `` Gayest नगर in अमेरिका '', in भाग because of the large विविधता of पब्लिक offices held, and Washington State गुजर a bill in 2012 allowing LGBT couples to निकाह.
Tacoma is प्रसिद्ध लिये the 1940 पतन of the टकोमा narrows सेतु.
Chula Vista ( ; ) is the second largest नगर in the San डिएगो metropolitan क्षेत्रफल, the सातवाँ largest नगर in दक्षिणी कैलिफ़ोर्निया, the fourteenth largest नगर in the राज्य of कैलिफ़ोर्निया, and the 77th-largest city in the संयुक्त राज्य.
the जनसांख्यिकी was 243,916 as of the 2010 जनसांख्यिकी.
स्तिथ बस इससे शहर San डिएगो and इससे the Mexican किनारा in the South खाड़ी प्रदेश of the महानगर क्षेत्रफल, the city is at the बीच of एक of the richest आर्थिक और culturally विविध zones in the United States.
chula Vista is so नामित because of इसके दर्शनीय स्थान between the सैन डिएगो Bay and coastal mountain foothills.
Founded in the जल्दी 19th सदी, fast population विकास रै recently been observed in the city.
As the second largest city in सैन Diego काउंटी, Chula Vista रै जल्दी become a destination popular to अनेक पर्यटकों.
Located in the नगर is एक of America 's few year-round संयुक्त राज्य ओलम्पिक Training centers और लोकप्रिय tourist destinations शामिल क्रिकेट Wireless Amphitheater, the chula Vista मरीना, और the Chula विस्टा Nature बीच.
metes and bounds is a system or method of describing जमीन, रियल property ( in contrast to निजी प्रॉपर्टी ) or रियल एस्टेट.
the प्रणाली रै महरूम प्रयुक्त in इंग्लैण्ड लिये अनेक सदियां, और is स्टिल used there in the परिभाषा of general सीमाएँ.
By कस्टम, it was लागू in the असली Thirteen colonies that became the United राज्य, and in many अन्य जमीन jurisdictions आधारित on अंग्रेज़ी आम law.
typically the प्रणाली uses physical features of the local भूगोल, साथ साथ directions और दूरियाँ, to define and describe the boundaries of a पार्सल of जमीन.
The सीमाएँ are वर्णित in a कार्यशील prose स्टाइल, working around the पार्सल in sequence, इससे a पाइंट of शुरूआत, returning वापस to the वही point ; compare साथ the मौखिक अनुष्ठान of धड़कन the bounds.
It may include सन्दर्भ to other adjoining parcels ( और their स्वामी ), और it, in फेरे, could also be referred to in बाद surveys.
at the समय the वर्णन is compiled, it may have been चिह्नित on the मैदान with स्थाई स्मारक लगाई where वहीँ were no उपयुक्त natural monuments.
the term `` metes '' refers to a boundary defined by the measurement of each सीधा run, निर्दिष्ट by a distance between the terminal अंक, and an अभिविन्यास or दिशा.
A दिशा may be a सरल compass bearing, or a precise अभिविन्यास संकल्पित by accurate सर्वेक्षण विधि.
the पद `` bounds '' refers to a more सामान्य boundary वर्णन, ऐसे as साथ a certain watercourse, a stone wall, an adjoining public सड़क way, or an existing भवन.
the प्रणाली is often used to define larger pieces of प्रॉपर्टी ( e.g. farms ), and राजनैतिक subdivisions ( e.g. town सीमाएँ ) where precise परिभाषा is नहीं जरूरी or would be दूर too महंगी, or previously designated boundaries can be incorporated into the description.
सर इसहाक़ Newton ( 25 दिसम्बर 164220 कूच 1727 ) was an अंग्रेज़ी physicist और गणितज्ञ who is widely regarded as one of the सबसे influential वैज्ञानिकों of सब समय और as a key figure in the scientific क्रान्ति.
उसके book Philosophiæ Naturalis प्रिन्सिपिया mathematica ( `` Mathematical सिद्धान्त of प्राकृतिक Philosophy '' ), पहला प्रकाशित in 1687, laid the मूलाधार लिये सबसे of शास्त्रीय mechanics.
न्यूटन भी बना seminal contributions to प्रकाशिकी and साझा क्रेडिट साथ गॉटफ्राइड लैबनिट्ज़ for the आविष्कार of the infinitesimal कलन.
Newton 's प्रिन्सिपिया formulated the कानून of गति और universal gravitation कि वर्चस्व scientists ' दृश्य of the शारीरिक ब्रह्मांड लिये the next तीन सदियां.
It भी demonstrated that the motion of objects on the धरती और that of celestial bodies could be वर्णित by the same principles.
by deriving कॅप्लर 's कानून of ग्रहीय गति इससे उसके mathematical description of गम्भीरता, न्यूटन removed the पिछला संदेह परिचय the validity of the heliocentric model of the ब्रह्मांड.
Newton निर्मित the पहला व्यावहारिक reflecting दूरदर्शी and विकसित a सिद्धान्त of रंग आधारित on the अवलोकन कि a प्रिज़्म decomposes white light into the अनेक colours of the दृश्य spectrum.
he also प्रतिपादित an empirical विधि of cooling और पढ़ाई the गति of sound.
in जोड to his कार्य on the कलन, as a गणितज्ञ न्यूटन contributed to the study of शक्ति series, generalised the द्विपद प्रमेय to non-integer exponents, और विकसित न्यूटन 's विधि for approximating the जड़ें of a फलन.
न्यूटन was a fellow of ट्रिनिटी कॉलेज and the second lucasian प्राध्यापक of गणित at the University of कैम्ब्रिज.
He was a devout but unorthodox ईसाई और, unusually लिये a सदस्य of the कैम्ब्रिज संकाय, he refused to take holy orders in the Church of इंग्लैण्ड, शायद because he privately rejected the doctrine of trinitarianism.
in जोड to उसके work on the गणितीय sciences, Newton भी dedicated much of उसके time to the study of alchemy and biblical कालक्रम, but सबसे of his कार्य in those areas remained unpublished जबतक long बाद his मौत.
In his later जीवन, न्यूटन became अध्यक्ष of the royal समाज.
He भी served the अंग्रेजों सरकारी as वार्डन और निपुण of the royal मिंट.
प्रोf. Walter lewin explains न्यूटन 's विधि of gravitation in MIT कोर्स 8.01
Satellites और projectiles सब obey Newton 's विधि of gravitation
Newton 's law of सार्वभौमिक gravitation राज्य कि every पाइंट द्रव्यमान in the universe attracts every अन्य पाइंट mass साथ a फ़ोर्स कि is सीधे आंशिक to the उत्पाद of उनके masses और inversely आंशिक to the वर्गाकार of the अलहदा between उन्हें.
( separately it थी shown कि विशाल spherically symmetrical masses attract और हैं attracted as if सब उनके mass were concentrated at their centers. )
इस is a general शारीरिक law निकला इससे अनुभवजन्य observations by कया न्यूटन called प्रेरण.
It is a part of classical यांत्रिकी और was प्रतिपादित in न्यूटन 's work Philosophiæ Naturalis प्रिन्सिपिया Mathematica ( `` the Principia '' ), पहला प्रकाशित on 5 July 1687.
( जब न्यूटन 's किताब थी प्रस्तुत in 1686 to the royal Society, Robert Hooke बना a अर्जी कि Newton था obtained the inverse वर्गाकार law इससे उसे – देखिए History section below. )
in आधुनिक भाषा, the विधि states the following:
Assuming si इकाई, f is measured in newtons ( n ), m1 and m2 in गामा ( kg ), r in मीटर ( m ), और the constant g is approximately बराबर to.
the मान of the निरंतर g was first accurately determined from the परिणाम of the कैवेंडिश प्रयोग conducted by the British वैज्ञानिक हेनरी कैवेंडिश in 1798, हालांकि Cavendish did नहीं खुद गणना a numerical value लिये g.
इस experiment थी also the पहला test of न्यूटन 's theory of gravitation between masses in the laboratory.
it took प्लेस 111 years बाद the प्रकाशन of Newton 's प्रिन्सिपिया और 71 years बाद न्यूटन 's मौत, so none of न्यूटन 's calculations could उपयोग the मान of g ; बजाय he could तभी गणना a फ़ोर्स सापेक्ष to another फ़ोर्स.
न्यूटन 's विधि of gravitation resembles Coulomb 's law of electrical शक्तियां, which is प्रयुक्त to गणना the magnitude of electrical फ़ोर्स between दो charged लाशें.
दोनो हैं inverse-square कानून, in which फ़ोर्स is inversely आंशिक to the वर्गाकार of the distance between the लाशें.
कूलम्ब 's Law has the product of two आरोप in प्लेस of the उत्पाद of the masses, and the electrostatic निरंतर in place of the गुरुत्वाकर्षक निरंतर.
Newton 's विधि रै चूंकि महरूम superseded by आइंस्टीन 's सिद्धान्त of सामान्य आपेक्षिकता, लकिन it continues to be used as an बेहतरीन सन्निकटन of the effects of गम्भीरता.
Relativity is required तभी जब there is a need लिये चरम परिशुद्धता, or when dealing with gravitation for extremely massive and घना वस्तुएँ.
White और रेड flags, representing इराकी और अमरीकी मौतों, बैठना in the ग्रास चतुष्कोण of the Valley पुस्तकालयों on the Corvallis, ऑरेगॉन, campus of ऑरेगॉन State University.
As part of the traveling इराकी देह गिनती प्रदर्शनी इससे 2008 to 2009 ( not related to इराकी Body Count प्रोजेक्ट ), the ध्वज aim to `` raise awareness of the human cost of the इराकी युद्ध. ''
( may 2008 )
हताहत of the conflict in इराकी चूंकि 2003 ( शुरूआत साथ the 2003 invasion of Iraq, और continuing साथ the ensuing occupation of इराकी, as खूब as the क्रियाएँ of the विभिन्न armed समूह operating in the देश ) have आइये in अनेक forms, और the सटीकता of the information उपलब्धियाँ on different types of इराकी युद्ध casualties varies greatly.
The तालिका नीचे summarizes various estimates of the इराकी casualty figures.
For troops in the u.s.-led multinational गठबन्धन, the death टोल is carefully tracked और अद्यतनीकृत daily, and the names और छायाचित्र of those killed in कार्रवाई as well as in accidents have been प्रकाशित widely.
A total of 4,486 u.S. सैनिको यहूद मारे in इराकी between 2003 and 2012.
Regarding the इराकी, however, सूचना on दोनो military and civilian casualties is both कम precise and less सतत.
estimates of casualty स्तर are available इससे reporters on the झाँकी, इससे officials of शामिल संगठन, और इससे समूह कि summarize information on incidents reported in the news media.
The शब्द `` हताहत `` in इसके सबसे general भाव includes the injured as खूब as the मुर्दे.
खाते of the क्रमांक of गठबन्धन wounded vary widely, partly क्युकी it is नहीं स्पष्ट कया चाहिए be counted : should only those चोटों गंभीर पर्याप्त to put a soldier out of आयोग be included ?
do illnesses or injuries caused by accidents गिनती, or should the फ़ोकस be restricted to wounds caused by शत्रु सगाई ?
स्त्रोत using different definitions may arrive at बहुत different संख्याएँ, और sometimes the precise परिभाषा is नहीं clearly specified.
asalto al coche ( Robbery of the कोच ), by फ्रांसिस्को de गोया
a highwayman थी a चोर और brigand जो preyed on travellers.
इस type of outlaw प्रायः travelled और robbed by horse, as compared to a footpad जो travelled और robbed on पैर.
आरोहित लुटेरों यहूद widely considered to be socially श्रेष्ठ to footpads.
ऐसे robbers संचालित in Great Britain और आयरलैंड from the elizabethan era जबतक the early 19th सदी.
the word highwayman is first ज्ञात to be used in the साल 1617 ; अन्य euphemisms included `` शूरवीरों of the road '' और `` सज्जनों of the सड़क. ''
दो शर्तें लागू to 19th-century उत्तर American highwaymen were road agents in कुछ instances for पहाड़ डाकुओं while in other मामले the पद is rlallaala for mountain-based ruffians.
in the वही समय period in ऑस्ट्रेलिया, they were known as bushrangers.
Earvin `` जादू '' Johnson, Jr. ( born August 14, 1959 ) is a रिटायर्ड अमरीकी professional basketball खिलाड़ी who played पाइंट guard for the लॉस एंजिल्स लेकर्स of the नेशनल बास्केट संघ ( NBA ).
बाद जीतना championships in ऊँची स्कूल and college, जॉनसन was selected पहला overall in the 1979 NBA ड्राफ्ट by the लेकर्स.
he जीती a चैंपियनशिप and an NBA फाइनल Most मूल्यवान Player Award in his रुकी season, और won चार अधिक championships साथ the लेकर्स दौरान the 1980s.
Johnson retired abruptly in 1991 बाद announcing कि he था contracted hiv, लकिन लौटे to खेल in the 1992 All-Star Game, जीतना the all-star mvp पुरस्कार.
After protests from उसके fellow players, he रिटायर्ड again लिये चार years, लकिन लौटे in 1996, at age 36, to play 32 खेल for the लेकर्स पहले retiring for the third और final time.
जॉनसन 's करियर उपलब्धियाँ शामिल तीन एनबीए MVP पुरस्कार, nine NBA फाइनल appearances, बारह all-star खेल, और टेन all-nba पहला and Second टोली nominations.
He led the लीग in regular-season assists four times, और is the NBA 's all-time leader in औसत assists per खेल, at 11.2.
जॉनसन was a member of the `` Dream Team ``, the U.S. basketball team कि जीती the ओलम्पिक सुनहरा पदक in 1992.
After leaving the एनबीए in 1992, जॉनसन formed the Magic जॉनसन All-Stars, a barnstorming टोली that travelled around the world playing exhibition खेल.
जॉनसन थी सम्मानित as एक of the 50 महानतम खिलाड़ी in एनबीए इतिहास in 1996, and enshrined in the बास्केट Hall of कीर्ति in 2002.
he was रेटेड the महानतम NBA पाइंट guard of सब time by ESPN in 2007.

allium cells in different phases of the कोशिका साईकिल
the कोशिकाएं of eukaryotes ( बाएँ ) और prokaryotes ( सही )
the cell is the मौलिक structural, functional और biological ईकाई of all ज्ञात living organisms.
It is the smallest unit of life कि is वर्गीकृत as a जीना thing ( except virus, जिससे consists तभी from dna/rna covered by protein और lipids ), और is often called the भवन ब्लाक of जीवन.
it consists of a protoplasm enclosed भीतर a membrane, जिससे contains many biomolecules ऐसे as प्रोटीन and nucleic acids.
Organisms can be classified as एककोशिकीय ( consisting of a सिंगल cell ; सहित सबसे जीवाणु ) or बहुकोशिकीय ( including plants और animals ).
While the number of कोशिकाएं in plants और पशु varies इससे प्रजाति to प्रजाति, इंसानो contain परिचय 100 trillion ( 1014 ) कोशिकाएं.
सबसे संयंत्र और एनिमल कोशिकाएं are between 1 और 100 micrometres and इसलिए are visible only अंतर्गत the microscope.
The कोशिका थी खोजा by रॉबर्ट hooke in 1665.
the cell theory, पहला developed in 1839 by Matthias jakob schleiden और Theodor schwann, states कि all जीवों हैं रचित of एक or अधिक कोशिकाएं, कि all कोशिकाएं आइये from preexisting कोशिकाएं, कि vital कृत्यों of an सजीव occur भीतर कोशिकाएं, and that सब cells contain the hereditary information जरुरी लिये regulating कोशिका functions और लिये transmitting information to the अगला पीढी of कोशिकाएं.
Cells उभरा on ग्रह Earth at least 4.0–4.3 अरब सालो पहले.
the शब्द कोशिका आता इससे the लैटिन cella, meaning `` छोटी रूम ''.
The वर्णनात्मक term for the smallest living biological ढांचा was coined by रॉबर्ट Hooke in a किताब he प्रकाशित in 1665 when he compared the कॉर्क कोशिकाएं he देखी through his सूक्ष्मदर्शी to the छोटी rooms भिक्षुओं lived in.
grecian Formula is a मेन 's hair coloring उत्पाद in the United राज्य.

a motor स्कूटर 's सामने साथ an अव्यवहारिक number और variety of headlamps, added for सजावटी purposes
a headlamp is a lamp attached to the सामने of a vehicle to लाइट the सड़क ahead.
headlamp प्रदर्शन has steadily improved throughout the automobile आयु, spurred by the ग्रेट disparity between दिन और nighttime ट्रैफ़िक fatalities : the u.S. नेशनल राजमार्ग Traffic Safety Administration राज्य कि nearly half of सब traffic-related fatalities occur in the अंधेरा, despite only 25 % of traffic यात्राएं during darkness.
While it is common for the term हेडलाइट to be प्रयुक्त interchangeably in informal discussion, headlamp is the term for the यंत्र itself, जबकि headlight properly refers to the beam of लाइट उत्पादित और वितरित by the device.
अन्य वाहनों, ऐसे as trains and aircraft, हैं required to have headlamps.
Bicycle headlamps are often used on साइकिल, और हैं जरूरी in कुछ jurisdictions.
वे can be powered by a battery or a छोटी विद्युत सृजनकर्ता on the व्हील.
additionally automotive रात्रि vision प्रणालियों work to supplement headlamps.
महिलाओं 's अधिकारों हैं the अधिकारों and entitlements claimed लिये महिलाओं और लड़कियों of many समाजों worldwide.
In कुछ स्थान ये rights हैं institutionalized or supported by विधि, local कस्टम, और आचरण, whereas in अन्य they may be ignored or suppressed.
वे differ from broader notions of human rights through claims of an inherent historical और traditional पूर्वाग्रह against the कसरत of अधिकारों by महिलाओं और लड़कियों in favour of men और लड़कों.
Issues commonly संबद्ध साथ notions of महिलाओं 's अधिकारों include, though are नहीं limited to, the सही : to bodily अखंडता and autonomy ; to vote ( suffrage ) ; to hold public दफ्तर ; to कार्य ; to fair मजदूरी or equal अदा ; to अपना प्रॉपर्टी ; to शिक्षा ; to serve in the military or be conscripted ; to enter into विधिक अनुबंध ; and to have marital, parental and धार्मिक अधिकारों.
Caryn ऐलेन जॉनसन, best ज्ञात as Whoopi गोल्डबर्ग (, ( born November 13, 1955 ) is an American comedienne, actress, singer-songwriter, political activist, लेखक और talk show मेजबान.
गोल्डबर्ग बना her film डेब्यू in The रंग जामुनी ( 1985 ), playing celie, a mistreated ब्लैक स्त्री in the Deep South.

इस प्रदर्शन जीती her a second Golden ग्लोब और an Academy पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन Supporting Actress ; this बना गोल्डबर्ग तभी the दूसरी ब्लैक स्त्री in the इतिहास of the Academy पुरस्कार to जीत an acting oscar—the first being हैटी McDaniel who जीती for गए साथ the हवा in 1939.

गोल्डबर्ग has महरूम मनोनीत लिये 13 Emmy Awards लिये her कार्य in टेलीविज़न.

वो is one of the few मनोरंजनकर्ता जो have won an एमी, Grammy, ऑस्कर, और टोनी पुरस्कार.
the नेशनल हॉकी लीग ( NHL ; ) is an `` unincorporated not-for-profit association '' which operates a major professional बर्फ hockey लीग of 30 franchised member clubs, of जिससे seven are currently located in Canada और 23 in the United राज्य.
Headquartered in नई यॉर्क नगर, the NHL is widely माना to be the premier professional ice हॉकी लीग in the world, और एक of the प्रमुख पेशेवर खेल लीग in the संयुक्त राज्य and Canada.
The Stanley कप, the oldest पेशेवर खेल ट्रॉफी in North America, is awarded annually to the लीग playoff champion at the समाप्त of each season.
The लीग was organized on November 26, 1917, in मॉन्ट्रियल, क्यूबेक, कनाडा, बाद the बर्खास्तगी of operations of its predecessor संगठन, the नेशनल हॉकी Association ( NHA ), which had महरूम संस्थापित in 1909.
it प्रारंभ with चार teams and, through a श्रेणी of expansions, contractions, और relocations, the लीग is now composed of 30 क्रियाशील franchises.
the स्वदेश to जिससे the name of the लीग originally referred was Canada, although the league has now been binational चूंकि 1924 when it विस्तारित into the United States.
बाद a श्रमिक dispute कि led to the cancellation of the संपूर्ण 2004–05 season, the लीग resumed play under a new सामूहिक bargaining अनुबंध that included a सैलरी cap.
in 2009, the NHL enjoyed रिकार्ड highs in terms of sponsorships, उपस्थिति, और टेलीविज़न audiences.
the NHL draws many अत्यधिक skilled खिलाड़ी इससे सब over the संसार and फिलहाल रै players from about 20 अलग देशों.
Although Canadians have historically constituted the बहुमत of the खिलाड़ी in the एनएचएल, over the पास्ट चार प्लस दशकों the percentages of us और European players have increased both because of the NHL 's continued विस्तार इससे six to तीस clubs चूंकि 1967, और the increased availability of अत्यधिक skilled यूरोपीय खिलाड़ी.
Maggots feeding on carrion.
a maggot is the larva of a मक्खी ( अनुक्रम diptera ) ; it is applied in particular to the लार्वे of Brachyceran उड़ता, ऐसे as houseflies, cheese उड़ता, and blowflies, rather than larvae of the Nematocera, ऐसे as मच्छरों और Crane flies.
`` Maggot '' is not a तकनीकी पद and should not be लिया as such ; in अनेक मानक पाठ्यपुस्तकों of कीटविज्ञान it does नहीं appear in the अनुक्रमणिका at all.
in many non-technical ग्रन्थ the पद is used for insect लार्वे in general.
Other स्त्रोत have coined उनके अपना definitions ; लिये उदाहरण : ``...
The पद applies to a grub जब सब ट्रेस of limbs has disappeared... '' and ``... Applied to the footless लार्वे of dipters. ''
Maggot-like मक्खी लार्वे are of चौड़ी importance in पारिस्थितिकी and आयुर्विज्ञान ; among other roles, विभिन्न प्रजाति are prominent in recycling carrion और garbage, attacking फसलों and foodstuffs, spreading सूक्ष्मजैविक infections, and causing myiasis.
हेरोदेस (, Hordos, यूनानी :, Hērōdēs ), also known as हेरोदेस the ग्रेट ( 73/74 BCE – 4 bce in जेरिको ), थी a रोमन क्लाएंट किंग of judea.
उसके epithet of `` the ग्रेट '' is widely विवादित as he is वर्णित as `` a madman जो murdered उसके own family और a ग्रेट अनेक rabbis ``.
he is भी ज्ञात लिये his colossal building प्रोजेक्ट in जेरूसलम and elsewhere, including his expansion of the दूसरी टेम्पल in Jerusalem ( sometimes referred to as हेरोदेस 's Temple ) और the निर्माण of the port at Caesarea Maritima.
महत्वपूर्ण details of his जीवनी are gleaned इससे the works of the 1st सदी CE roman–jewish historian josephus Flavius.
The Romans बना Herod 's बेटे, हेरोदेस archelaus, ethnarch of judea, samaria, and Idumea ( biblical edom ) इससे 4 bce to 6 CE, referred to as the tetrarchy of Judea.
Archelaus थी judged incompetent by the रोमन सम्राट Augustus जो तब संयुक्त samaria, Judea proper और Idumea into iudaea प्रांत अंतर्गत rule of a prefect until आयु 41.
हेरोदेस 's other बेटे हेरोदेस antipas थी tetrarch of galilee इससे 4 bce–39 CE.
ABO रक्त समूह antigens present on red blood कोशिकाएं और igm antibodies उपस्थित in the सीरम
The abo रक्त समूह प्रणाली is the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण blood type system ( or रक्त समूह system ) in इंसान रक्त transfusion.
the associated anti-a and anti-B antibodies are प्रायः igm antibodies, जिससे are प्रायः produced in the first years of जीवन by sensitization to पर्यावरणीय substances such as food, जीवाणु, और वाइरस.
abo blood प्रकार हैं भी present in कुछ other पशु, लिये example apes ऐसे as chimpanzees, bonobos, and gorillas.

Brett lorenzo favre ( born अक्तूबर 10, 1969 ) is a former American football quarterback who खर्च the majority of उसके करियर साथ the ग्रीन Bay Packers of the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल League ( एनएफएल ).
he was a 20-year veteran of the एनएफएल, having निभाई क्वार्टरबैक for the Atlanta falcons ( 1991 ), ग्रीन खाड़ी पैकर्स ( 1992 – 2007 ), New यॉर्क jets ( 2008 ) and Minnesota वाइकिंग्स ( 2009 – 2010 ).
favre is the तभी quarterback in एनएफएल इतिहास to throw for over 70,000 yards, over 500 touchdowns, over 300 interceptions, over 6,000 completions, and over 10,000 pass कोशिशें.
favre प्रारंभ at the quarterback position लिये the University of Southern Mississippi for चार सालो पहले being चयनित in the second गोलाकार of the 1991 एनएफएल ड्राफ्ट by अटलांटा ( 33rd overall ).
he थी traded to ग्रीन खाड़ी on February 10, 1992, लिये the 19th चुनें in the 1992 NFL Draft.
Favre became the Packers ' starting क्वार्टरबैक in the चौथी game of the 1992 ऋतु, stepping in लिये injured क्वार्टरबैक डॉन majkowski, and started every game through the 2007 ऋतु.
He थी traded to the नई York Jets and प्रारंभ at क्वार्टरबैक लिये the 2008 ऋतु पहले signing साथ the Vikings on अगस्त 18, 2009 as their starting क्वार्टरबैक.
He made an एनएफएल रिकार्ड 297 लगातार starts ( 321 सहित playoffs ).
he is the तभी player to जीत the ap सबसे मूल्यवान खिलाड़ी तीन consecutive टाइम्स ( 1995–97 ).
he रै led टीमों to eight प्रभाग championships ( 1995, 1996, 1997, 2002, 2003, 2004, 2007, 2009 ), पाँच NFC चैंपियनशिप खेल ( 1995, 1996, 1997, 2007, 2009 ), and two सुपर Bowl appearances ( सुपर Bowl xxxi, सुपर Bowl xxxii ), winning एक ( सुपर कटोरी xxxi ).
he holds many एनएफएल रिकॉर्ड, सहित most करियर touchdown passes, most career गुजर गज, सबसे career pass completions, most करियर pass कोशिशें, most career interceptions thrown, सबसे consecutive starts by a खिलाड़ी, सबसे लगातार starts by a क्वार्टरबैक, most career victories as a starting क्वार्टरबैक, सबसे sacked, और most fumbles.
He is भी referred to by his उपनाम `` the Gunslinger ''.

the World चौड़ी वेब ( abbreviated as WWW or W3, commonly known as the web ), is a प्रणाली of interlinked हाइपरटेक्स्ट दस्तावेज़ पहुँचा via the Internet.
साथ a वेब browser, एक can view वेब पृष्ठों that may contain text, images, वीडियो, और other multimedia, and navigate between them via hyperlinks.
Using अवधारणाओं from उसके पहले hypertext प्रणालियों like enquire, अंग्रेजों engineer, कंप्यूटर वैज्ञानिक और at that समय employee of the cern, सर टिम berners-lee, अभी निदेशक of the संसार Wide Web consortium ( w3c ), wrote a प्रस्ताव in March 1989 लिये what होता eventually become the World Wide वेब.
at cern, a European शोध संगठन near जेनेवा straddling the किनारा between France और Switzerland, Berners-Lee और belgian कंप्यूटर scientist रॉबर्ट Cailliau प्रस्तावित in 1990 to use हाइपरटेक्स्ट `` to कड़ी और access सूचना of विभिन्न kinds as a वेब of nodes in जिससे the उपयोक्ता can ब्राउज़ at होगा '', and they सरेआम introduced the प्रोजेक्ट in दिसम्बर of the same year.
Wayne Lyman Morse ( October 20, 1900july 22, 1974 ) थी a राजनेता and attorney इससे ऑरेगॉन, संयुक्त राज्य, ज्ञात लिये उसके proclivity लिये opposing उसके पार्टियों ' leadership, और specifically for his opposition to the वियतनाम युद्ध on संवैधानिक grounds.
born in मैडिसन, विस्कॉन्सिन, और educated at the University of wisconsin-madison और the विश्वविद्यालयों of मिनेसोटा विधि स्कूल, मोर्स moved to Oregon in 1930 and began शिक्षण at the विश्वविद्यालयों of ऑरेगॉन स्कूल of विधि.
दौरान World युद्ध ii he थी निर्वाचित to the संयुक्त राज्य सीनेट as a Republican ; he became an स्वतंत्र बाद ड्वाइट D. Eisenhower 's चुनाव to the प्रेसिडेंसी in 1952.
जबकि an स्वतंत्र, he नियत a record लिये performing the second longest one-person filibuster in the इतिहास of the सीनेट.
Morse joined the लोकतांत्रिक Party in 1955, and was reelected twice while a सदस्य of that party.
मोर्स बना a brief run लिये the लोकतांत्रिक Party 's अध्यक्षीय nomination in 1960.
a few years later, मोर्स थी one of तभी two सीनेटरों who opposed the गल्फ of tonkin रेज़ोल्यूशन, which प्राधिकृत the अध्यक्ष to लो सैन्य कार्रवाई in वियतनाम बगैर a declaration of war.
He continued to बोलो आउट against the युद्ध in the ensuing years, और खोया his 1968 बोली लिये reelection to bob Packwood, जो criticized उसके दमदार opposition to the युद्ध.
Morse बना two अधिक बोलियों लिये reelection to the Senate पहले his मौत in 1974.
in parliamentary कार्यविधि, a motion to table has दो different और contradictory अर्थs:
In the संयुक्त राज्य, to table usually means the to lay [ the टॉपिक ] on the तालिका or to move लिये postponement of विचार ; a प्रस्ताव to बर्खास्तगी विचार of a pending motion.
much कम often, it अर्थात् a गति to `` put on the table '' : a प्रस्ताव to शुरू विचार ( or reconsideration ), a उपयोग सतत with the बाकी of the english-speaking संसार.
in the rest of the english-speaking संसार ऐसे as the United किंगडम, to table means to मूव to प्लेस [ the topic ] upon the तालिका ( or to मूव to प्लेस on the table ) : a proposal to begin विचार ( or reconsideration ) of a proposal.
दोनो the American और the British dialects have the भाव of `` to तालिका '' as to lay [ the टॉपिक ] on the table or to कारण [ the topic ] to झूठ on the तालिका.
the अंतर is the विचार of कया the तालिका is for, कि of a shelf off to the पक्ष, or an active work बेंच.
the British meaning रै the भाव of the table as होने an क्रियाशील work बेंच, साथ the टॉपिक होने the center of ध्यान, माना और discussed by सब until it can be resolved, at which point it is लिया बंद the 'table '.
the अमरीकी sense is कि the तालिका is जैसे that of a शेल्फ, archive, or long-term भंडार device, जहाँ the टॉपिक रै महरूम disposed of by sending it to the 'table ' और leaving it वहीँ.
Toy स्टोरी 3 is a 2010 अमरीकी 3d कंप्यूटर एनिमेटेड comedy-drama prison film, and the third installment in the खिलौना स्टोरी series.
It was उत्पादित by Pixar Animation studios और वितरित by Walt Disney Pictures.
निर्देशित by ली Unkrich, the film थी released worldwide from जून through October in डिज़्नी डिजिटल 3-D, RealD, और imax 3d.
खिलौना Story 3 was भी the first film to be released theatrically with dolby घेर 7.1 sound.

The प्लाट focuses on the खिलौने Woody, बज़ Lightyear, और उनके friends dealing साथ an अनिश्चित future as their owner, Andy, prepares to छोड़ लिये college.
अभिनेताओं Tom Hanks, टिम एलन, जोन Cusack, Don rickles, estelle हैरिस, John Ratzenberger, Wallace Shawn, जेफ़ pidgeon, Jodi बेंसन, R. ली ermey, जॉन मॉरिस, and लॉरी metcalf reprised their voice-over roles from the previous films.
Jim Varney, जो निभाई slinky श्वान in the first दो films, और जो ranft, जो portrayed lenny and Wheezy, both died पहले production began on खिलौना Story 3.
the भूमिका of Slinky श्वान was taken over by ब्लेक क्लार्क ( a friend of varney ), जबकि Ranft 's characters and various others यहूद लिखा आउट of the स्टोरी.
New वर्ण include performances by Ned beatty, Timothy डाल्टन, क्रिस्टन schaal, bonnie Hunt, whoopi गोल्डबर्ग, जेफ़ garlin, Richard दयालु, और माइकल Keaton.
the feature broke Shrek the तिहाई record as the biggest खोलने day उत्तर अमरीकी सकल लिये an एनिमेटेड फिल्मी unadjusted लिये महंगाई, और a big opening with an unadjusted सकल of $ 110,307,189.

This is the highest-grossing फिल्मी of 2010, both in the संयुक्त States और Canada, and विश्वव्यापी.
in जल्दी August, it became Pixar 's highest-grossing film at the उत्तर American बक्सा दफ्तर ( surpassing ढूंढना Nemo ), and the highest-grossing एनिमेटेड फिल्मी of all समय विश्वव्यापी ( surpassing shrek 2 ) ; बाद that माह, खिलौना स्टोरी 3 became the first कभी animated film in इतिहास to make over $ 1 billion विश्वव्यापी.
it is currently the 10th-highest-grossing फिल्मी of सब समय.

जॉन Levell starks ( born August 10, 1965 ) is an अमरीकी रिटायर्ड पेशेवर basketball शूटिंग गार्ड.

Secure डिजिटल or ( sd ) is a non-volatile memory कार्ड स्वरूप लिये use in पोर्टेबल devices, such as मोबाईल phones, डिजिटल कैमरे, gps नेविगेशन devices, और tablet कंप्यूटर.
the Secure डिजिटल मानक is कायम by the SD कार्ड Association ( sda ).
SD technologies have महरूम implemented in अधिक than 400 ब्रांड्स across dozens of उत्पाद श्रेणी and more than 8,000 मॉडल.
The Secure Digital स्वरूप includes four card परिवारों available in three अलग रूप कारकों.
the चार families हैं the असली standard-capacity ( SDSC ), the High-Capacity ( SDHC ), the eXtended-Capacity ( sdxc ), और the sdio, which combines input/output functions with आंकड़ा storage.
the तीन रूप factors हैं the original size, the `` mini '' आकार, और the `` सूक्ष्म '' size ( see illustration ).
There are अनेक combinations of form factors और device परिवारों.
electrically passive adapters allow the use of a छोटी कार्ड in a मेजबान यंत्र निर्मित to hold a larger card.
Host devices कि comply साथ newer संस्करण of the specification provide पिछड़ा compatibility and accept पुरानी sd cards, लकिन इस article explains अनेक कारकों कि can prevent the use of a newer SD card:
A नए card may offer greater क्षमता than the मेजबान यंत्र can handle.
a newer card may उपयोग a संचिका system the मेजबान यंत्र can not navigate.
Use of an SDIO कार्ड requires the मेजबान device be designed लिये the input/output कृत्यों the कार्ड provides.
the संगठन of the कार्ड थी changed starting साथ the sdhc परिवार.
कुछ vendors produced SDSC cards ऊपर 1 gb before the SDA था मानकीकृत a विधि of doing so.
the sda उपयोग several trademarked logos to enforce compliance साथ इसके विशेषताएँ and assure users of संगतता.
Hugh जॉन Mungo ग्रान्ट ( born 9 सितंबर 1960 ) is a British कर्ता और फिल्मी निर्माता.
he has प्राप्त a सुनहरी Globe, a BAFTA, and an Honorary césar.
His films have earned अधिक than US $ 2.4 billion इससे 25 नाट्य releases विश्वव्यापी.
ग्रान्ट हासिल अंतरराष्ट्रीय स्टारडम बाद appearing in रिचर्ड Curtis 's कामयाब Four विवाह और a अंत्येष्टि ( 1994 ).
He प्रयुक्त इस breakthrough भूमिका as a बारंबार cinematic persona during the 1990s, delivering कॉमिक प्रदर्शन in mainstream films like Mickey ब्लू आँखें ( 1999 ) और नॉटिंग Hill ( 1999 ).
By the फेरे of the 21st सदी, he had स्थापित खुद as a अग्रणी man skilled with a satirical कॉमिक talent.
Grant रै विस्तारित उसके oeuvre साथ critically acclaimed turns as a cad in ब्रिजेट जोन्स 's Diary ( 2001 ), परिचय A Boy ( 2002 ), प्रेम Actually ( 2003 ), and अमरीकी Dreamz ( 2006 ).
He बाद निभाई विरूद्ध प्रकार with multiple कैमियो भूमिकाएँ in the एपिक drama film Cloud Atlas ( 2012 ).
Within the film उद्योग, Grant is cited as an anti-film स्टार जो approaches his भूमिकाएँ like a अक्षर कर्ता, और attempts to मेक उसके acting appear spontaneous.
hallmarks of उसके comic कौशल include a nonchalant टच of विडंबना / sarcasm और पढ़ाई शारीरिक mannerisms as well as उसके precisely-timed dialogue delivery and फेशियल expressions.
the entertainment मीडिया 's coverage of ग्रान्ट 's जीवन बंद the बिग screen रै प्रायः निष्प्रभ his work as a thespian.
he रै महरूम vocal परिचय उसके disrespect लिये the व्यवसायिक of एक्टिंग, और in उसके तिरस्कार towards the culture of हस्ती and दुश्मनी towards the media.
In a करियर spanning 30 years, ग्रान्ट has repeatedly claimed कि acting is not a true कॉलिंग लकिन बस a जॉब he गिरी into.
the हान राजवंश ( ; ) ( 206 BC – 220 AD ) was an इम्पीरियल dynasty of चीन, preceded by the qin राजवंश ( 221–207 bc ) and succeeded by the तीन Kingdoms ( 220–280 ad ).
it थी संस्थापित by the विद्रोही नेता लियू Bang, ज्ञात मरणोपरांत as सम्राट gaozu of Han.
It was briefly बाधित by the Xin राजवंश ( 9–23 AD ) of the पूर्व रीजेंट वांग mang.
This interregnum separates the हान into दो periods : the पश्चिमी हान ( 206 bc – 9 AD ) and Eastern Han ( 25–220 AD ).
Spanning over four centuries, the काल of the हान राजवंश is considered a सुनहरी age in चाइनीज history.
To इस दिन, चीन 's बहुमत जातीय group refers to itself as the `` Han people '' and the चाइनीज स्क्रिप्ट is referred to as `` हान वर्ण ``.
The हान Empire was विभाजित into क्षेत्रों directly controlled by the central सरकारी, ज्ञात as commanderies, and a क्रमांक of semi-autonomous kingdoms.
These kingdoms gradually खोया सब vestiges of their independence, particularly following the विद्रोह of the Seven States.
the xiongnu, a nomadic confederation जिससे वर्चस्व the पूर्वी यूरेशियाई स्तान, defeated the Han फौज in battle in 200 BC.
Following the defeat, a राजनैतिक विवाह गठबंधन थी negotiated in which the हान became the de facto अवर partner.
When, despite the सन्धि, the xiongnu जारी to raid हान सीमायें, सम्राट wu of हान ( r. 141–87 bc ) शुभारम्भ several military अभियान against उन्हें.
the ultimate हान विजय in ये युद्धों आखिरकार मजबूर the Xiongnu to accept vassal औकात as हान tributaries.
ये campaigns expanded हान sovereignty into the tarim जलाशय of Central Asia and helped स्थापित the vast व्यापार network ज्ञात as the रेशा Road, which reached as दूर as the भूमध्यसागरीय संसार.
हान शक्तियां प्रबंधित to divide the Xiongnu into दो competing राष्ट्र, the दक्षिणी और उत्तरी xiongnu, and मजबूर the उत्तरी Xiongnu आरपार the इली River.
despite ये victories, the territories उत्तर of हान 's सीमायें यहूद जल्दी overrun by the nomadic Xianbei कनफेडरेशन.
After 92 AD, the राजमहल हिजड़े increasingly involved themselves in court राजनीती, engaging in violent power struggles between the विभिन्न consort clans of the empresses और सम्राज्ञी dowagers, causing the हान 's ultimate downfall.
इम्पीरियल authority थी भी seriously challenged by large daoist धार्मिक societies जिससे instigated the पीला पगड़ी Rebellion और the पाँच pecks of Rice विद्रोह.
following the death of सम्राट ling ( r. 168–189 ad ), the palace हिजड़े suffered होलसेल massacre by military अधिकारियों, allowing सदस्यों of the aristocracy और military राज्यपालों to become warlords और divide the साम्राज्य.
जब Cao pi, King of वेई, usurped the सिंहासन from Emperor Xian, the Han राजवंश ceased to मौजूद.
the हान राजवंश थी an age of आर्थिक समृद्धि और saw a significant विकास of the धन अर्थव्यवस्था पहला established during the झोऊ राजवंश ( c. 1050–256 BC ).
the coinage जारी by the सेंट्रल सरकारी मिंट in 119 bc remained the मानक coinage of चीन जबतक the Tang Dynasty ( 618–907 ad ).
to pay लिये इसके military अभियान और the उपनिवेश of newly conquered frontier territories, the government राष्ट्रीयकृत the निजी नमक और iron उद्योग in 117 bc.
ये सरकारी monopolies were repealed during the Eastern हान काल, and the खोया आय was recouped through heavily taxing निजी entrepreneurs.
the emperor थी at the pinnacle of हान समाज.
He presided over the Han government लकिन shared शक्ति with दोनो the nobility और नियुक्त मंत्रियों जो आए largely इससे the scholarly gentry क्लास.
From the reign of सम्राट wu onward, the चाइनीज अदालत officially sponsored confucianism in शिक्षा और अदालत राजनीती, synthesized साथ the cosmology of later विद्वानों such as डांग Zhongshu.
इस नीति endured until the fall of the चिंग Dynasty in 1911 ad.
Science and प्रौद्योगिकी दौरान the Han period देखी significant advances, सहित papermaking, the nautical steering rudder, the use of negative संख्याएँ in गणित, the raised-relief map, the हाइड्रोलिक -powered armillary गोला लिये खगोलशास्त्र, and a भूकम्पमापी employing an उलट pendulum.
Tourette syndrome ( भी पुकारा tourette 's syndrome, Tourette 's विकार, गाइल्स de la tourette सिंड्रोम, gts or, more commonly, बस tourette 's or TS ) is an inherited neuropsychiatric disorder with onset in बाल्यकाल, characterized by अनेक शारीरिक ( motor ) tics और at least एक vocal ( phonic ) tic.
ये tics characteristically मोम and wane, can be suppressed temporarily, and are preceded by a premonitory urge.
Tourette 's is पारिभाषित as part of a वर्णक्रम of tic विकार, जिससे शामिल क्षणिक and chronic tics.
Tourette 's थी once माना a विरल और bizarre syndrome, सबसे often associated with the exclamation of obscene शब्द or socially अनुचित और अपमानजनक remarks ( coprolalia ), लकिन इस लक्षण is present in तभी a small अल्पसंख्यक of people साथ tourette 's.
tourette 's is no longer considered a विरल condition, लकिन it is नहीं सदा correctly पहचाना because most मामले हैं mild और the severity of tics decreases लिये सबसे children as they pass through adolescence.
between 0.4 % and 3.8 % of children आयु 5 to 18 may have tourette 's ; the prevalence of क्षणिक और दीर्घकालिक tics in school-age children is higher, with the अधिक आम tics of eye blinking, खाँसी, गला clearing, sniffing, and फेशियल movements.
चरम tourette 's in adulthood is a rarity, and tourette 's करता not adversely affect intelligence or life प्रत्याशा.
जेनेटिक और पर्यावरणीय कारकों play a भूमिका in the etiology of tourette 's, लकिन the exact कल्याणकारी हैं unknown.
in सबसे cases, दवा is unnecessary.
वहीँ is no प्रभावी उपचार for प्रत्येक case of tics, but निश्चित medications और therapies can सहायता जब उनके उपयोग is warranted.
Education is an important part of any उपचार plan, and explanation and reassurance अलोन हैं often sufficient उपचार.
comorbid conditions ( co-occurring diagnoses अन्य than tourette 's ) ऐसे as attention-deficit अतिसक्रियता disorder ( ADHD ) और obsessive–compulsive विकार ( ओसीडी ) are उपस्थित in अनेक मरीजों देखी in tertiary specialty clinics.
ये अन्य शर्तें often cause more कार्यात्मक पुतलियों to the व्यक्तिगत than the tics कि हैं the hallmark of tourette 's, hence it is important to correctly पहचानो comorbid शर्तें and दावत उन्हें.
the eponym थी bestowed by Jean-Martin charcot ( 1825–1893 ) on निमित्त of उसके निवासी, जॉर्जेस अल्बर्ट Édouard ब्रूटस गाइल्स de la tourette ( 1859–1904 ), a French चिकित्सक और neurologist, who published an account of नौ patients with tourette 's in 1885.
Sunbeam बैज.
सनबीम थी a marque पंजीकृत by John Marston Co. Ltd of wolverhampton, England, in 1888.
the company पहला बना साइकिल, then motorcycles and गाड़ियाँ from the लेट 19th सदी जबतक about 1936, और लागू the marque to all तीन forms of परिवहन.
The कम्पनी भी manufactured aero इंजन in the First संसार War और 647 वायुयान during the दूसरी संसार युद्ध.

फॉक्स News Channel ( fnc ), भी ज्ञात as फॉक्स न्यूज, is a केबल news चैनल स्वामित्व by the फॉक्स entertainment समूह, a subsidiary of News निगम.

the mandibular पहला molar or six-year molar is the दाँत located distally ( away इससे the midline of the फेस ) इससे दोनो the mandibular दूसरी premolars of the मुँह but mesial ( toward the midline of the फेस ) इससे दोनो mandibular दूसरी molars.
it is located on the mandibular ( lower ) मेहराब of the मुँह, and generally opposes the maxillary ( upper ) पहला molars and the ऊर्ध्वहनु 2nd premolar in normal क्लास I occlusion.
The function of इस molar is समान to कि of all molars in लिहाज़ to grinding being the प्रिंसिपल कार्रवाई during mastication, commonly known as chewing.
There are प्रायः पाँच well-developed पुलिन on mandibular पहला molars : two on the buccal ( side nearest the गाल ), two lingual ( पक्ष निकटतम the जीभ ), and एक distal.
There are ग्रेट मतभेद between the deciduous ( baby ) mandibular molars और those of the permanent mandibular molars, भी though their फलन are समान.
The permanent mandibular molars are नहीं माना to have any teeth कि precede it.
despite होने नामित molars, the पतझड़ी molars are followed by permanent premolars.
In the universal प्रणाली of संकेतन, the पतझड़ी mandibular first molars are designated by a अक्षर written in अपरकेस.
the right पतझड़ी mandibular पहला molar is ज्ञात as `` S '', और the बाएँ एक is ज्ञात as `` L ''.
the अंतरराष्ट्रीय संकेतन has a different प्रणाली of संकेतन.
यूँ, the right पतझड़ी mandibular first molar is ज्ञात as `` 84 '', और the left one is known as `` 74 ''.
in the universal system of notation, the स्थाई mandibular first molars are designated by a number.
The right स्थाई mandibular पहला molar is ज्ञात as `` 30 '', and the बाएँ one is ज्ञात as `` 19 ''.
the पामर notation उपयोग a क्रमांक in conjunction with a symbol designating in जिससे quadrant the दाँत is मिला.
लिये इस दाँत, the बाएँ and सही पहला molars would have the वही number, `` 6 '', but the सही एक होता have the प्रतीक, `` ┐ '', over it, जबकि the बाएँ एक होता have, `` ┌ ''.
the international संकेतन रै a different numbering प्रणाली than the previous two, और the right permanent mandibular पहला molar is ज्ञात as `` 46 '', और the बाएँ एक is ज्ञात as `` 36 ''.
mandibular प्राथमिक पहला molars usually have चार गूदा horns.
The पहला molar is usually the पहला स्थाई tooth to erupt और रै वयस्क undertones.
anatomy : the mandibular पहला molar has five cusps : the mesiobuccal ( mb, toward midline और cheek ), mesiolingual ( ML, toward midline and tongue ), distolingual ( DL, दूर from midline and towards जीभ ), distobuccal ( DB, दूर from midline and toward cheek ), और distal ( d, दूर इससे midline ), सूचीबद्ध in अनुक्रम of अवरोहण आकार.
सूचीबद्ध in अनुक्रम of अवरोहण ऊँचाई वे are : ml, dl, df, mf, और D. an आठवीं cusp थी मिला in a प्राथमिक second निम्नतर molar in an Argentinean चाइल्ड.
viewed from the top of the tooth ( occlusal दृश्य ), the mandibular first molar is pentagonal ( पाँच sided ) in shape and tapers toward the lingual, साथ the sides होने the buccal सतह, the mesial सतह, the lingual surface, distal सतह, और the distobuccal सतह.
The occlusal surface रै चार grooves.
the सेंट्रल नाली is not सीधा लकिन runs bas the बीच of the दाँत mesially to distally और contains चार गड्ढों ( mesial, central, सेंट्रल, और distal ).
The distobuccal नाली रनों इससे the distal गड्ढे in the central नाली distobuccally separating the distal और distobuccal cusps.
The lingual groove रनों इससे the अधिक distal of the central गड्ढों in the सेंट्रल नाली toward the lingual सतह between the mesiolingual और distolingual पुलिन.
the buccal नाली runs इससे the more mesial of the central गड्ढों in the central नाली toward the buccal surface between the mesiobuccal and distobuccal पुलिन समाप्ति in the buccal गड्ढे.
the portion of the central groove between the सेंट्रल pits is termed the लुईस offset और is अनिवार्य to खाता लिये the locations of the buccal and lingual डोले ( buccal नाली होने अधिक mesial than the lingual groove जबकि वे हैं समानांतर ).
From the buccal ( buccal दृश्य ), दो जड़ें are present.
the distal रूट is generally straighter, although both प्रायः have a पतला distal गोलाई.
the heights of रुपरेखा on the mesial और distal सम्पर्क the सटा दांत and हैं located at the junction of the occlusal और मध्य तिहाई of the क्राउन.

porcupines are rodents with a कोट of शार्प कांटे, or quills, कि बचाव और camouflage उन्हें इससे परभक्षी.
वे are indigenous to the Americas, दक्षिणी Asia, and अफ़्रीकी.
Porcupines हैं the तीसरा largest of the rodents, पीछे the capybara और the बीवर.
सबसे porcupines हैं परिचय long, with an long tail.
Weighing, वे are rounded, large और slow.
porcupines आइये in various shades of brown, धूसर, और the unusual श्वेत.
Porcupines ' spiny सुरक्षा resembles that of the unrelated erinaceomorph hedgehogs और monotreme echidnas.
the आम porcupine is a herbivore.
it eats leaves, herbs, टहनियों and ग्रीन plants जैसे skunk गोभी and clover और in the शीत it may खा छाल.
The उत्तर अमरीकी साही प्रायः climbs trees to ढूँढें खाना.
the अफ़्रीकी porcupine is not a climber और forages on the मैदान.
it is ज़्यादातर nocturnal, but होगा sometimes forage for खाना in the day.
porcupines have become a pest in Kenya और हैं खाया as a कोमलता.
The name साही आता from Middle French porc espin ( spined pig ).
a क्षेत्रीय American नाम लिये the animal is quill pig.

इलियास J. मैककॉय ( may 2, 1844 – October 10, 1929 ) थी a black canadian-american आविष्कारक और इंजीनियर, जो थी notable लिये his 57 u.S. patents, सबसे to do साथ lubrication of steam इंजन.

A हाइड्रोजन vehicle is a गाडी that उपयोग hydrogen as इसके onboard fuel लिये motive शक्ति.
Hydrogen वाहनों शामिल हाइड्रोजन fueled स्पेस rockets, as खूब as automobiles और other transportation वाहनों.
The शक्ति पौधे of ऐसे वाहनों बदलें the chemical उर्जा of hydrogen to mechanical उर्जा either by burning hydrogen in an आतंरिक दहन इंजन, or by reacting हाइड्रोजन साथ ऑक्सीजन in a fuel कोशिका to चलाएं इलेक्ट्रिक motors.
फैली उपयोग of hydrogen for fueling परिवहन is a key तत्व of a प्रस्तावित हाइड्रोजन economy.
हाइड्रोजन ईंधन does नहीं occur naturally on धरती and यूँ is नहीं an उर्जा सोर्स ; rather it is an उर्जा carrier.
It is सबसे अक्सर बना from methane or other चट्टान fuels, लकिन it can be produced using स्त्रोत ( such as हवा, सौर, or नाभिकीय ) कि are intermittent, too व्याप्त or too cumbersome to directly propel वाहनों.
Integrated wind-to-hydrogen plants, using electrolysis of जल, are exploring technologies to deliver costs कम enough, and quantities ग्रेट पर्याप्त, to compete साथ परंपरागत energy sources.
अनेक companies हैं working to develop technologies that might efficiently exploit the संभावित of हाइड्रोजन उर्जा लिये mobile uses.
The attraction of using हाइड्रोजन as an energy currency is that, if hydrogen is prepared बगैर using चट्टान ईंधन inputs, गाडी propulsion would नहीं contribute to carbon dioxide emissions.
the drawbacks of hydrogen use हैं ऊँची capital cost, कम energy content per ईकाई आवाज़, high tankage weights, बहुत ऊँची भंडार vessel pressures, the भंडार, transportation and filling of गैसीय or liquid हाइड्रोजन in vehicles, the large investment in infrastructure कि would be जरूरी to ईंधन वाहनों, and the inefficiency of उत्पादन प्रक्रियाओं.
sacramento is the पूंजी city of the U.S. state of California और the seat of सरकारी of sacramento काउंटी.
it is located at the संगम of the Sacramento नदी और the अमरीकी नदी in the northern portion of कैलिफ़ोर्निया 's expansive Central Valley.
With an अनुमानित 2011 population of 477,891, it is the sixth-largest नगर in कैलिफ़ोर्निया और the 35th largest city in the संयुक्त राज्य.
Sacramento is the core सांस्कृतिक और आर्थिक center of the sacramento महानगर क्षेत्रफल which includes सात counties साथ an estimated 2009 population of 2,527,123.
इसके महानगर क्षेत्रफल is the चौथी largest in कैलिफ़ोर्निया बाद the वृहद लॉस एंजिल्स क्षेत्रफल, सैन Francisco खाड़ी क्षेत्रफल, और the सैन Diego महानगर क्षेत्रफल, as खूब as the 25th largest in the संयुक्त States.
sacramento was cited by Time पत्रिका as अमेरिका 's most ethnically और racially integrated नगर in 2002.
Sacramento became a नगर through the efforts of the स्विस immigrant जॉन Sutter, sr., उसके son जॉन Sutter, Jr., और जेम्स W. मार्शल.
sacramento grew जल्दी thanks to the सुरक्षा of sutter 's Fort, जिससे थी established by sutter in 1839.
दौरान the California सुनहरा Rush, Sacramento was a प्रमुख distribution पाइंट, a commercial और agricultural बीच, and a टर्मिनस लिये वैगन trains, stagecoaches, riverboats, the टेलीग्राफ, the टट्टू एक्स्प्रेस, and the पहला Transcontinental Railroad.
कैलिफ़ोर्निया State विश्वविद्यालयों, sacramento, अधिक commonly ज्ञात as sacramento राज्य or सैक राज्य, is the largest लोकल विश्वविद्यालयों.
it is one of the twenty-three campuses of the कैलिफ़ोर्निया राज्य विश्वविद्यालयों system.

स्टीवन पॉल `` Steve '' कार्य ( ; फ़रवरी 24, 1955 – October 5, 2011 ) was an American entrepreneur and inventor, बेहतरीन known as the co-founder, chairman, और सीईओ of ठहराना inc.
Through Apple, he was widely recognized as a charismatic पायोनियर of the निजी computer क्रान्ति और लिये उसके influential career in the कंप्यूटर और उपभोक्ता इलेक्ट्रॉनिक्स फ़ील्ड, transforming `` एक उद्योग बाद another, from computers और स्मार्टफ़ोन to music और फिल्मों... ''
Jobs भी co-founded and परोसा as मुख्य कार्यपालिका of पिक्चर्स एनिमेशन Studios ; he became a सदस्य of the फलक of निर्देशकों of The वॉल्ट Disney Company in 2006, when डिज़्नी acquired पिक्चर्स.

The रोमन numeral system is a cousin of etruscan numerals.
उपयोग of Roman numerals continued after the decline of the Roman साम्राज्य.
From the 14th century on, रोमन numerals began to be replaced in सबसे contexts by more convenient hindu-arabic numerals ; however इस प्रक्रम थी क्रमिक, और the उपयोग of Roman numerals in कुछ नाबालिग applications continues to इस day.
Effective नाभिकीय चार्ज Diagram
The effective nuclear चार्ज ( often symbolize as or Z* ) is the net धनात्मक चार्ज अनुभवी by an इलेक्ट्रॉन in a multi-electron atom.
The पद `` प्रभावी '' is used because the shielding effect of negatively charged electrons रोकता उच्चतर orbital electrons from experiencing the पूरा नाभिकीय charge by the repelling effect of inner-layer electrons.
the प्रभावी nuclear चार्ज अनुभवी by the outer shell electron is भी called the कोर charge.
It is संभावित to determine the strength of the नाभिकीय चार्ज by looking at the ऑक्सीकरण number of the अणु.

meister means master in जर्मनी ( as in निपुण craftsman, or as an honorific शीर्षक ऐसे as meister Eckhart ).
The शब्द is akin to maestro.
In खेल, meister is प्रयुक्त for the current नेशनल, European or संसार champion ( Deutscher Meister, *europameister, Weltmeister ).
Many modern दिन जर्मनी police forces उपयोग the शीर्षक meister.
During the Second World War, meister थी the उच्चतम आयोजिक rank of the ordnungspolizei.
meister रै been borrowed into अंग्रेज़ी कठबोली, जहाँ it is प्रयुक्त in यौगिक nouns.
a व्यक्ति referred to as “meister” is एक जो रै extensive सैद्धांतिक ज्ञान and practical कौशल in उसके व्यवसायिक, business, or कुछ other kind of work or activity.
For उदाहरण, a “puzzle-meister” होता be someone अत्यधिक skilled at solving पहेलियाँ.

एडगर allan Poe ( born Edgar पो ; जनवरी 19, 1809 – अक्तूबर 7, 1849 ) was an अमरीकी लेखक, कवि, एडिटर और literary critic, considered भाग of the अमरीकी रोमांटिक Movement.
Best known लिये his tales of mystery और the घोर, Poe was एक of the earliest अमरीकी practitioners of the छोटी स्टोरी and is generally माना the आविष्कारक of the detective fiction genre.
He is further credited साथ contributing to the emerging genre of science fiction.
he थी the first well-known अमरीकी लेखक to कोशिश to earn a जीना through लिखने अलोन, resulting in a financially difficult जीवन और career.
he थी born as Edgar Poe in Boston, Massachusetts ; he थी orphaned यंग when उसके mother died shortly बाद his पिता abandoned the परिवार.
Poe was लिया in by जॉन and Frances Allan, of रिचमंड, वर्जिनिया, but वे never formally अपनाया him.
He attended the विश्वविद्यालयों of वर्जिनिया लिये एक semester but बाएँ due to lack of money.
After enlisting in the Army और बाद failing as an अधिकारी 's cadet at West पाइंट, पो parted तरीके साथ the Allans.
His publishing करियर began humbly, साथ an बेनाम collection of कविताएं, tamerlane and अन्य कविताएं ( 1827 ), credited only to `` a bostonian ''.
पो switched his फ़ोकस to गद्य और खर्च the next अनेक सालो working लिये literary जर्नल्स और periodicals, बनने known लिये उसके own style of साहित्यिक आलोचना.
उसके work मजबूर उसे to move among अनेक cities, including Baltimore, Philadelphia, and New यॉर्क नगर.
in Baltimore in 1835, he शादीशुदा वर्जिनिया clemm, his 13-year-old cousin.
In January 1845 Poe published his poem, `` The रेवेन ``, to instant कामयाबी.
उसके बीवी died of tuberculosis दो years बाद इसके प्रकाशन.
He began planning to उपज उसके अपना journal, the penn ( बाद renamed The स्टाइलस ), though he died पहले it could be उत्पादित.
on October 7, 1849, at age 40, Poe died in बाल्टीमोर ; the cause of उसके death is अनजान और रै महरूम variously attributed to दारू, दिमाग जमघट, cholera, दवाएँ, दिल disease, rabies, आत्महत्या, तपेदिक, और other agents.
पो और उसके works influenced साहित्य in the संयुक्त राज्य और around the संसार, as well as in specialized फ़ील्ड, ऐसे as cosmology and क्रिप्टोग्राफी.
Poe and his work appear throughout लोकप्रिय संस्कृति in साहित्य, music, films, और टेलीविज़न.
a number of his घरों हैं समर्पित संग्रहालय आज.
the Mystery Writers of अमेरिका उपस्थित an सालाना award ज्ञात as the एडगर पुरस्कार लिये distinguished कार्य in the रहस्य genre.
शेर हैं obligate carnivores ; they require up to seven kilograms ( 15 पाउंड ) of मांस प्रति day.
A प्रमुख component of their diet is the flesh of large mammals, जैसे इस अफ़्रीकी buffalo.
A carnivore ( ) अर्थ 'meat eater ' ( लैटिन, caro अर्थ 'meat ' or 'flesh ' and vorare अर्थ 'to devour ' ) is an सजीव that गर्भाशयी इसके उर्जा and nutrient requirements from a आहार consisting मुख्यतः or exclusively of एनिमल ऊतक, whether through predation or scavenging.
पशु कि निर्भर solely on animal flesh for their nutrient आवश्यकताएँ are माना carnivores while those कि भी consume non-animal food हैं माना carnivores.
omnivores भी consume both एनिमल और non-animal खाना, and अलावा इससे the more सामान्य definition, there is no clearly पारिभाषित ratio of संयंत्र to animal material कि होता distinguish a facultative carnivore इससे an सर्वाहारी.
a carnivore that sits at the शीर्ष of the foodchain is an apex परभक्षी.
पौधे कि कैप्चर and digest कीट हैं called मांसाहारी plants.
Similarly, fungi कि कैप्चर microscopic पशु are often called मांसाहारी fungi.
The फीफा World Cup, प्रायः बस the World Cup, is an अंतरराष्ट्रीय association फ़ुटबॉल competition contested by the वरिष्ठ men 's नेशनल teams of the सदस्यों of Fédération internationale de Football Association ( FIFA ), the खेल 's वैश्विक शासी body.
the चैंपियनशिप रै महरूम awarded प्रत्येक four सालो चूंकि the inaugural टूर्नामेंट in 1930, मगर in 1942 and 1946 जब it was not आयोजित क्युकी of the Second संसार युद्ध.
the वर्तमान champions are Spain, जो जीती the 2010 टूर्नामेंट.
the वर्तमान स्वरूप of the टूर्नामेंट involves 32 टीमों competing लिये the शीर्षक at venues भीतर the मेजबान nation ( s ) over a period of परिचय a month ; इस phase is प्रायः called the संसार कप Finals.
A योग्यता phase, which फिलहाल takes प्लेस over the preceding तीन सालो, is used to determine जिससे टीमों qualify for the tournament साथ साथ the मेजबान nation ( s ).
The 19 संसार कप tournaments have महरूम won by आठ अलग national teams.
Brazil have जीती पाँच times, और वे are the तभी team to have played in प्रत्येक टूर्नामेंट.
The अन्य संसार कप विजेता हैं Italy, with four titles ; जर्मनी, with तीन शीर्षक ; अर्जेंटीना और inaugural विजेता Uruguay, with two शीर्षक each ; और England, France, और Spain, with one शीर्षक each.
the World Cup is the world 's सबसे widely viewed sporting इवेंट ; an अनुमानित 715.1 लाख लोगों देखी the final match of the 2006 FIFA World कप आयोजित in जर्मनी.
The next three संसार Cups होगा be hosted by Brazil in 2014, रूस in 2018, और क़तर in 2022.
Heroes is an American विज्ञान fiction टेलीविज़न drama series created by टिम Kring कि appeared on एनबीसी for four सीज़न from सितंबर 25, 2006 through February 8, 2010.
the series tells the कहानियां of ordinary people who discover superhuman abilities, और how ये abilities take प्रभाव in the वर्ण ' lives.
The series emulates the aesthetic स्टाइल and storytelling of अमरीकी comic books, using multi-episode story arcs that निर्माण upon a larger, more encompassing arc.
the श्रेणी was produced by tailwind प्रोडक्शन्स in संघ साथ Universal Media studios.
It was फिल्माया primarily in लॉस एंजिल्स, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
चार complete seasons aired, ending on फ़रवरी 8, 2010.
The critically acclaimed पहला season था a चलाएं of 23 episodes और garnered an औसत of 14.3 million viewers in the United States, receiving the highest दरजा लिये an एनबीसी नाटक प्रीमियर in five years.
The दूसरी season of नायक attracted an average of 13.1 million viewers in the U.S., and marked एनबीसी 's एकमात्र श्रेणी among the शीर्ष 20 क्रमित कार्यक्रम in कुल viewership लिये the 2007–2008 ऋतु.
नायक रै अर्जित a number of पुरस्कार और nominations, including Primetime एमी पुरस्कार, Golden ग्लोब्स, लोगों 's चुनाव Awards और अंग्रेजों अकादमी टेलीविज़न Awards.
An online एक्सटेंशन of the series, नायक 360 Experience, later rebranded as Heroes Evolutions, थी निर्मित to explore the Heroes ब्रह्मांड and provides इनसाइट into the show 's mythology.

NBC घोषित नायक cancellation on May 14, 2010.

जॉन Pierpont `` J. P. ''
Morgan ( अप्रैल 17, 1837 – कूच 31, 1913 ) थी an American फाइनेंसर, बैंकर, लोकसेवक and आर्ट collector who dominated corporate finance और industrial consolidation दौरान उसके time.
in 1892 Morgan arranged the merger of Edison General इलेक्ट्रिक और Thomson-Houston Electric कम्पनी to रूप General इलेक्ट्रिक.
बाद financing the creation of the संघीय स्टील Company, he मिलाया in 1901 साथ the कार्नेगी Steel Company and अनेक अन्य स्टील and आयरन businesses, including Consolidated स्टील and तार कम्पनी स्वामित्व by William edenborn, to रूप the संयुक्त राज्य Steel Corporation.
Morgan died in रोम, इटली, in his sleep in 1913 at the age of 75, leaving उसके सौभाग्य और business to his बेटे, John pierpont `` जोकर '' Morgan, jr., and bequeathing his mansion and विशाल किताब collections to The मॉर्गन पुस्तकालयों & संग्रहालय in New यॉर्क.
at the height of मॉर्गन 's करियर during the जल्दी 1900s, he and उसके partners था वित्तीय निवेश in अनेक large corporations and यहूद accused by critics of controlling the स्वदेश 's ऊँची finance.
he directed the बैंकिंग coalition that रोका the दहशत of 1907.
he was the leading financier of the प्रगतिशील era, and his समर्पण to दक्षता and modernization helped रूपांतरण अमरीकी कारोबार.
