डिजिटल forensics ( sometimes known as डिजिटल forensic science ) is a शाखा of forensic science encompassing the recovery और investigation of material found in डिजिटल डिवाइस, प्रायः in संबंध to कंप्यूटर अपराधों.
The पद डिजिटल forensics थी originally प्रयुक्त as a synonym for कंप्यूटर forensics लकिन रै विस्तारित to cover छानबीन of all devices capable of storing डिजिटल आंकड़ा.
साथ जड़ें in the निजी कम्प्यूटिंग क्रान्ति of the लेट 1970s और जल्दी '80s, the discipline विकसित in a haphazard manner दौरान the 1990s, और it थी नहीं जबतक the जल्दी 21st century कि national नीतियों उभरा.
Digital forensics investigations have a किस्में of अनुप्रयोग.
the most आम is to support or खण्डन a hypothesis पहले दण्ड or civil ( as भाग of the इलेक्ट्रॉनिक डिस्कवरी process ) न्यायालयों.
Forensics may also विशेषता in the private sector ; such as during internal कॉरपोरेट investigations or intrusion investigation ( a विशेषज्ञ जांच into the nature और extent of an unauthorized संजाल intrusion ).
The तकनीकी aspect of an investigation is विभाजित into अनेक sub-branches, relating to the प्रकार of digital डिवाइस शामिल ; computer forensics, network forensics, forensic आंकड़ा विश्लेषण and मोबाईल device forensics.
The ठेठ forensic प्रक्रम encompasses the seizure, forensic इमेजिंग ( acquisition ) और विश्लेषण of डिजिटल मीडिया और the उत्पादन of a रपट into एकत्रित प्रमाण.
as well as identifying direct evidence of a अपराधों, डिजिटल forensics can be प्रयुक्त to attribute evidence to विशिष्ट संदिग्धों, confirm alibis or कथन, determine intent, पहचानो स्त्रोत ( लिये उदाहरण, in कापीराइट cases ), or authenticate documents.
Investigations हैं much broader in पैमाना than other क्षेत्रों of forensic analysis ( जहाँ the usual उद्देश्य is to provide answers to a श्रेणी of simpler सवाल ) प्रायः involving complex time-lines or hypotheses.
A तुलना of the chromaticities enclosed by कुछ color स्पेसेस.
A रंग मॉडल is an abstract गणितीय मॉडल describing the रास्ता colors can be represented as tuples of संख्याएँ, typically as three or four मान or रंग components ( e.g. RGB and CMYK are color मॉडल ).
however, a color मॉडल with no associated mapping function to an निरपेक्ष color space is a अधिक or less arbitrary color प्रणाली with no कनेक्शन to any globally समझा प्रणाली of color interpretation.
adding a निश्चित मानचित्रण फलन between the color model and a निश्चित सन्दर्भ रंग स्पेस परिणाम in a definite `` footprint '' भीतर the सन्दर्भ color space.
इस `` footprint '' is ज्ञात as a gamut, and, in संयोजन with the color मॉडल, defines a नई color space.
लिये उदाहरण, Adobe RGB और srgb हैं दो अलग निरपेक्ष रंग स्पेसेस, both आधारित on the RGB मॉडल.
In the सबसे generic भाव of the परिभाषा ऊपर, color स्पेसेस can be पारिभाषित बगैर the उपयोग of a color model.
These स्पेसेस, such as Pantone, are in प्रभाव a दिए नियत of names or संख्याएँ जिससे हैं defined by the अस्तित्व of a सम्बन्धित नियत of शारीरिक रंग swatches.

मजदूर Day is an अमरीकी संघीय अवकाश observed on the first Monday in September, कि celebrates the आर्थिक और सोशल योगदान of मजदूर.
जीवन बीमे is a contract between an insured ( बीमे policy होल्डर ) और an insurer, जहाँ the insurer promises to pay a designated लाभार्थी a योग of धन ( the `` लाभ '' ) upon the death of the insured व्यक्ति.
Depending on the contract, अन्य events ऐसे as टर्मिनल बीमारी or नाजुक बीमारी may भी ट्रिगर payment.
the नीति होल्डर typically pays a premium, either regularly or as a lump sum.
अन्य खर्च ( ऐसे as अंत्येष्टि खर्च ) हैं also sometimes included in the लाभ.
Life नीतियों हैं विधिक contracts and the terms of the अनुबंध describe the सीमाएं of the insured events.
Specific exclusions are often written into the अनुबंध to सीमा the liability of the insurer ; आम उदाहरण हैं claims relating to suicide, धोखाधड़ी, युद्ध, riot और सिविल commotion.
life-based contracts tend to पतन into दो प्रमुख categories:
Protection नीतियों – designed to provide a लाभ in the इवेंट of निर्दिष्ट event, typically a lump sum भुगतान.
a आम form of इस डिज़ाइन is term बीमे.
Investment policies – जहाँ the main उद्देश्य is to facilitate the विकास of पूंजी by नियमित or single प्रीमियम.
Common forms ( in the US ) are whole जीवन, सार्वभौमिक life और variable जीवन नीतियों.

Mitzi gaynor Donahue ( born may 2, 1962 in yorba Linda, Orange काउंटी, कैलिफ़ोर्निया ) is an American actress, भी credited and अधिक popularly known as Mitzi kapture.
Kapture began उसके करियर in films, सबसे of which यहूद not विशाल commercial सफलताओं.

The Xbox 360 is the दूसरी वीडियो खेल कंसोल विकसित by and उत्पादित for Microsoft और the successor to the Xbox.
The एक्सबॉक्स 360 competes with Sony 's PlayStation 3 और Nintendo 's वी as भाग of the seventh generation of वीडियो खेल consoles.
As of सितंबर 30, 2012, 70 लाख Xbox 360 consoles have been बेची worldwide.
the एक्सबॉक्स 360 was officially अनावरण on एमटीवी on may 12, 2005, साथ विस्तृत लॉन्च और खेल सूचना divulged बाद that month at the इलेक्ट्रॉनिक entertainment एक्सपो ( e3 ).
the console बेची आउट completely upon रिलीज in सब regions मगर in जापानी.
अनेक प्रमुख features of the Xbox 360 हैं इसके एकीकृत Xbox Live service कि allows खिलाड़ी to compete online ; download आर्केड खेल, खेल demos, trailers, tv shows, म्यूज़िक और फिल्मों ; और इसके खिड़कियाँ मीडिया बीच मल्टीमीडिया सामर्थ्य.
The एक्सबॉक्स सजीव also offers access to विभिन्न ( प्रायः region-specific ) third-party media स्ट्रीमिंग applications.
at their E3 presentation on जून 14, 2010, microsoft घोषित a redesigned Xbox 360 कि would ship on the वही day.
the redesigned console is slimmer than the previous एक्सबॉक्स 360 मॉडल और सुविधाएँ एकीकृत 802.11 b/g/n wi-fi, toslink S/PDIF optical audio आउटपुट, पाँच usb 2.0 पोर्ट ( compared to the तीन from पुरानी versions ) and a खास aux port.
पुरानी models of the एक्सबॉक्स 360 have since महरूम discontinued.

A backpack ( भी called रूकसाक, knapsack, packsack, पैक ) is, in इसके सरलतम रूप, a cloth sack carried on एक 's वापस और secured साथ two straps that go over the कन्धों, लकिन there can be अपवाद.
lightweight types of backpacks हैं sometimes worn on तभी एक shoulder डोरी.
Backpacks हैं प्रायः preferred to हैंडबैग for carrying भारी loads or carrying any sort of उपकरण, because of the limited क्षमता to carry भारी weights लिये long अवधि of time in the हैंड्स.
Large backpacks, used to carry loads over 10 kg ( 22 lbs ), usually offload the largest भाग ( up to परिचय 90 % ) of their वज़न onto padded हिप बेल्ट, leaving the shoulder straps mainly लिये stabilising the load.
इस improves the potential to carry heavy loads, as the कूल्हों are stronger than the कन्धों, and भी increases चपलता और संतुलन, चूंकि the लोड यात्राएँ nearer the wearer 's अपना बीच of द्रव्यमान.
in प्राचीन टाइम्स, the backpack was प्रयुक्त as a means to carry the शिकारी 's larger खेल और अन्य प्रकार of prey और as a रास्ता of easier transport लिये अन्य सामग्री.
in the मामले of larger hunts, the hunters would dismember their शिकार and वितरित the pieces of the एनिमल around, प्रत्येक एक पैकिंग the मांस into अनेक wrappings और then into बैग which वे लगाई on to their backs.
the bag itself was बना up of अलग animal छुपा और स्किन ( depending on कया sorts of पशु यहूद in the क्षेत्रफल ) और sewn together by the आंतों of कहा पशु, which यहूद woven साथ tightly to मेक a sturdy thread-like material.
Mexico ( ; ; ), officially the संयुक्त मैक्सिकन States ( ), is a federal संवैधानिक गणतंत्र in उत्तर अमेरिका.
It is bordered on the north by the United States ; on the दक्षिण और वेस्ट by the प्रशांत समंदर ; on the southeast by Guatemala, Belize, and the caribbean Sea ; और on the east by the Gulf of मैक्सिको.
covering लगभग two लाख वर्गाकार किलोमीटर ( over 760,000 sq mi ), मैक्सिको is the पांचवां largest country in the americas by total क्षेत्रफल and the 13th largest स्वतंत्र स्वदेश in the world.
With an estimated population of over 113 लाख, it is the world 's eleventh most populous country और the most populous spanish-speaking country.
Mexico is a संघ comprising thirty-one राज्य and a संघीय ज़िला, the capital नगर.
in pre-Columbian मैक्सिको अनेक संस्कृतियों matured into उन्नत civilizations ऐसे as the Olmec, the toltec, the teotihuacan, the Zapotec, the Maya और the Aztec पहले first सम्पर्क with europeans.
in 1521, स्पेन conquered and colonized the territory इससे इसके base in méxico-tenochtitlan, which थी administered as the viceroyalty of New Spain.
This territory would eventually become Mexico following मान्यता of the उपनिवेश 's स्वतंत्रता in 1821.
the post-independence period was characterized by आर्थिक instability, the Mexican-American युद्ध और territorial cession to the United States, a civil युद्ध, दो empires और a घरेलू dictatorship.
The latter led to the मैक्सिकन Revolution in 1910, जिससे culminated साथ the promulgation of the 1917 संविधान और the emergence of the देश 's वर्तमान political प्रणाली.
Elections आयोजित in जुलाई 2000 चिह्नित the first समय that an opposition party जीती the प्रेसिडेंसी from the संस्थागत क्रांतिकारी पार्टी.
चूंकि 2006 the देश has महरूम in the midst of a drug war which रै caused 60,000 deaths.
Mexico रै एक of the संसार 's largest economies, and is considered दोनो a क्षेत्रीय power and मध्य शक्ति.
in जोड, मैक्सिको was the पहला लैटिन American सदस्य of the Organisation for Economic co-operation and विकास OECD ( since 1994 ), and माना an upper-middle income देश by the World बैंको.
मैक्सिको is considered a newly industrialized country and an emerging शक्ति.
it has the fourteenth largest नाममात्र जीडीपी और the eleventh largest जीडीपी by purchasing शक्ति पैरिटी.
The अर्थव्यवस्था is strongly linked to those of इसके North American फ़्री Trade अनुबंध ( nafta ) साझेदार, especially the संयुक्त राज्य of अमेरिका.
Mexico बाँधने छठे in the संसार and पहला in the Americas by क्रमांक of युनेस्को संसार विरासत Sites with 31, and in 2007 थी the दसवाँ most visited देश in the संसार with 21.4 लाख अंतरराष्ट्रीय arrivals प्रति साल.
बेब Ruth holds the एमएलबी करियर slugging percentage रिकार्ड (.690 ).
in बेसबॉल आंकडे, slugging percentage ( abbreviated SLG ) is a लोकप्रिय माप of the power of a hitter.
it is गणना as कुल bases divided by at bats :
जहाँ ab is the क्रमांक of at-bats लिये a given player, and 1B, 2b, 3B, और hr हैं the क्रमांक of singles, doubles, triples, और घर रनों, क्रमशः.
Walks are specifically excluded इससे इस calculation.
For example, in 1920, बेब रुथ निभाई his पहला season लिये the नई York Yankees.
In 458 at bats, Ruth था 172 हिट्स, comprising 73 singles, 36 युगल, 9 तिगुना, and 54 घर runs, जिससे brings the total आधार गिनती to ( 73 × 1 ) + ( 36 × 2 ) + ( 9 × 3 ) + ( 54 × 4 ) = 388.
His कुल number of bases ( 388 ) divided by his total at-bats ( 458 ) is.847, his slugging प्रतिशत for the ऋतु.
the next year he slugged.846, और ये records गई अखंड until 2001, जब बैरी Bonds हासिल 411 bases in 476 at-bats, bringing his slugging percentage to.863, बेमेल since.
is a role-playing वीडियो game विकसित and published by वर्गाकार ( now Square Enix ) लिये the सुपर Nintendo Entertainment प्रणाली in 1995.
Chrono Trigger 's development टोली शामिल तीन designers कि Square dubbed the `` सपना टोली '' : hironobu Sakaguchi, the निर्माता of वर्गाकार 's फाइनल काल्पनिक श्रेणी ; yuji Horii, a freelance designer और निर्माता of Enix 's लोकप्रिय Dragon Quest series ; और अकिरा toriyama, a freelance manga कलाकार famed लिये उसके कार्य with ड्रैगन Quest and ड्रैगन बॉल.
kazuhiko Aoki उत्पादित the game, masato काटो wrote सबसे of the plot, जबकि composer yasunori mitsuda scored most of the game पहले गिरना ill and deferring remaining ट्रैक्स to फाइनल काल्पनिक composer nobuo uematsu.
The game 's स्टोरी follows a group of adventurers जो सफर through समय to prevent a वैश्विक catastrophe.
वर्गाकार re-released a ported संस्करण by Tose in जापानी लिये Sony 's PlayStation in 1999, later repackaged with a फाइनल काल्पनिक IV बंदरगाहों as फाइनल काल्पनिक Chronicles in 2001 लिये the North अमरीकी market.
a slightly enhanced Chrono Trigger थी released लिये the Nintendo ds on नवम्बर 25, 2008, in उत्तर अमेरिका and Japan, and गई on sale in ऑस्ट्रेलिया on February 3, 2009 और in यूरोपीय on February 6, 2009.
the game थी never released in PAL territories before the निन्टेंडो ds संस्करण.
Chrono ट्रिगर was a critical and commercial कामयाबी upon रिलीज and is considered today to be एक of the महानतम वीडियो खेल of all समय.
निन्टेंडो Power magazine वर्णित पहलुओं of chrono ट्रिगर as क्रांतिकारी, including इसके multiple endings, plot-related sidequests focusing on character विकास, unique battle system, और detailed ग्राफिक्स.
chrono Trigger थी the तीसरा best-selling खेल of 1995, and the game 's snes और प्लेस्टेशन iterations have shipped 2.65 million नक़ल as of कूच 2003.
the version लिये the Nintendo ds बेची 790,000 नक़ल as of कूच 2009.
chrono Trigger was also ported to मोबाईल phones, आभासी कंसोल, the PlayStation संजाल ( only in the यूएसए ), iOS डिवाइस, और एंड्रॉइड devices.
Goat चीज
Goat cheese, or chèvre ( इससे the French शब्द लिये goat ), is चीज बना आउट of the मिल्क of goats.
अतिताप is elevated देह तापमान due to विफल thermoregulation कि occurs when a देह produces or absorbs more ऊष्मा than it dissipates.
Extreme temperature उन्नयन then becomes a medical आपात requiring तात्कालिक उपचार to prevent disability or death.
The most आम causes शामिल heat stroke और प्रतिकूल प्रतिक्रियाएँ to दवाएँ.
The पूर्व is an अधि temperature उन्नयन caused by exposure to excessive ऊष्मा, or combination of ऊष्मा and humidity, कि overwhelms the heat-regulating mechanisms.
The latter is a अपेक्षाकृत rare side effect of many दवाएँ, विशेषकर those that affect the सेंट्रल nervous प्रणाली.
malignant hyperthermia is a विरल complication of कुछ types of सामान्य एनेस्थीसिया.
अतिताप can also be deliberately induced using दवाएँ or चिकित्सा डिवाइस and may be प्रयुक्त in the treatment of कुछ kinds of कर्कट और other शर्तें, most commonly in संयोजन with radiotherapy.
अतिताप differs इससे fever in that the body 's temperature set पाइंट remains अपरिवर्तित.
the opposite is hypothermia, which occurs जब the तापमान बूंदें नीचे that जरूरी to maintain सामान्य metabolism.
बेलीज़, is a country स्तिथ on the northeastern coast of Central अमेरिका.
It is the तभी देश in the क्षेत्रफल जहाँ अंग्रेज़ी is the आधिकारिक भाषा, हालांकि kriol and स्पेनी हैं अधिक commonly spoken.
बेलीज़ is bordered on the north by मैक्सिको, to the दक्षिण and west by Guatemala और to the ईस्ट by the Caribbean Sea.
Its मेनलैंड is about long और wide.
साथ of land और a population of तभी 312,698 निवासियों ( 2010 जनसांख्यिकी ), बेलीज़ possesses the न्यूनतम population density in सेंट्रल America.
the country 's population विकास रेट of 3.15 % ( 2012 est. ) is the दूसरी highest in the region and एक of the उच्चतम in the पश्चिमी गोलार्ध.
Belize 's abundance of terrestrial and समुद्री species, and its विविधता of ecosystems दे it a कुंजी प्लेस भीतर the globally significant Mesoamerican biological Corridor.
Belize रै a विविध समाज, comprising many संस्कृतियों and languages.
it is the तभी nation in the प्रदेश with a अंग्रेजों औपनिवेशिक विरासत, लकिन as a भाग of the Western caribbean Zone, it भी साझा a आम heritage साथ the fellow anglophone caribbean countries.
in सामान्य, बेलीज़ is considered to be a सेंट्रल American and Caribbean स्वदेश साथ दमदार ties to both the Caribbean और लैटिन अमेरिका.
Belize is a सदस्य of the Caribbean Community ( caricom ), the Community of Latin American and caribbean States ( celac ), and Central American Integration प्रणाली ( SICA ).
बेलीज़ is known for its सितंबर जश्न, और is the birthplace of चबाने गम और punta चट्टान.
The `` Betsy रॉस '' flag
a `` Betsy Ross '' flag उड़ती बाहर San फ्रांसिस्को City हॉल
the Betsy Ross flag is an early डिज़ाइन of the ध्वज of the संयुक्त राज्य, popularly attributed to बेट्सी रॉस, using the आम motifs of प्रत्यावर्ती red-and-white striped field with five-pointed stars in a ब्लू canton.
the flag थी designed दौरान the American Revolution और सुविधाएँ 13 stars to represent the original 13 colonies.
the distinctive विशेषता of the Ross ध्वज is the arrangement of the stars in a वृत्त.
हालांकि the बेट्सी रॉस स्टोरी is accepted by most अमेरिकी, some ध्वज इतिहासकारों and revisionists do नहीं accept the बेट्सी रॉस design as the पहला American ध्वज.
According to the traditional खाता, the असली ध्वज थी बना in जून 1776, जब a छोटी committee—including जार्ज वॉशिंगटन, रॉबर्ट मॉरिस and सापेक्ष जार्ज Ross —visited Betsy और discussed the need लिये a new American ध्वज.
बेट्सी स्वीकृत the job to manufacture the ध्वज, altering the कमेटी 's design by replacing the six-pointed stars with five-pointed सितारों.
While the बेट्सी Ross legend is questionable, the flag डिज़ाइन is ज्ञात to have महरूम in use by 1777 ; अल्फ्रेड b. Street वर्णित it at the आत्मसमर्पण of General Burgoyne और समझा the वृत्त of stars to represent equality among the अमरीकी राज्य.
It is one of the oldest versions of u.S. ध्वज known to मौजूद ; जबकि it is not the oldest surviving ध्वज centuries in cloth रूप, its likeness appears on पुरानी शारीरिक अरबिंदो, namely, the समकालीन रणभूमि paintings by जॉन trumbull और चार्ल्स Willson Peale.
वे depict the गोलाकार star व्यवस्था being flown इससे जलयान masts और अनेक other places, और यूँ provide the first ज्ञात historical दस्तावेज़ीकरण of the ध्वज 's रूप.
the मुहर of the u.S. विभाग of Veterans Affairs उपयोग the बेट्सी रॉस flag to represent service to all दिग्गजों from the अमरीकी Revolution to the उपस्थित दिन.
the बेट्सी Ross design of 13-star US ध्वज रै महरूम प्रदर्शित in अनेक लोकप्रिय artworks ( sometimes inaccurately, as in वॉशिंगटन क्रासिंग the डेलावेयर ) and films, such as the 1960 version of pollyanna.
The flag continues to be एक of the सबसे लोकप्रिय प्रतीकों of the American क्रान्ति.
a purr is a sound बना by all species of felids और is a part of cat संचार.
it varies between cats ( लिये example by loudness और टोन ), and इससे species to species, लकिन can be characterized as a tonal गुलजार.
the पद `` purring '' रै been प्रयुक्त liberally in साहित्य, और it has been claimed कि viverrids ( सीविट, mongoose, genet ), bears, badgers, hyaenas ( et cetera ) purr.
अन्य animals कि have been कहा to purr are खरगोश, squirrels, guinea सूअर, tapirs, ring-tailed lemurs, elephants, raccoons और gorillas जबकि खाने.
However, using a सख्त definition of purring that निरन्तर ध्वनि उत्पादन जरूर alternate between pulmonic egressive और ingressive airstream ( and usually go on for minutes ), पीटर्स ( 2002 ), in an exhaustive review of the वैज्ञानिक साहित्य, पहुँचे the निष्कर्ष कि जबतक then तभी ‘purring cats’ ( फ़ेलिडाए ) और दो species of genets, genetta tigrina, और सबसे likely also genetta genetta, had महरूम प्रलेखित to purr.
the platypus ( Ornithorhynchus anatinus ) is a semiaquatic स्तनधारी endemic to पूर्वी ऑस्ट्रेलिया, सहित Tasmania.
Together साथ the four प्रजाति of echidna, it is one of the five extant species of monotremes, the only mammals that lay eggs instead of giving जनम.
it is the एकमात्र जीना प्रतिनिधि of its family ( ornithorhynchidae ) और genus ( Ornithorhynchus ), हालांकि a number of सम्बन्धित प्रजाति have been found in the fossil रिकार्ड.
the असामान्य रूप of this egg-laying, duck -billed, beaver -tailed, otter -footed स्तनधारी baffled यूरोपीय naturalists when they first encountered it, साथ some considering it an elaborate धोखाधड़ी.
It is एक of the few venomous स्तनधारियों, the पुरूष platypus having a spur on the हिन्द पैर that delivers a venom capable of causing severe पीड़ा to इंसानो.
the unique features of the platypus मेक it an important विषय in the पढ़ाई of विकासवादी जीवविज्ञान and a recognisable and iconic प्रतीक of ऑस्ट्रेलिया ; it रै appeared as a शुभंकर at नेशनल कार्यक्रम और is प्रदर्शित on the रिवर्स of its 20-cent coin.
The platypus is the animal emblem of the state of New South वेल्स.
जबतक the जल्दी 20th century, it थी hunted लिये इसके फर, लकिन it is now protected throughout its range.
Although captive breeding programmes have था only सीमित success और the platypus is vulnerable to the effects of pollution, it is नहीं अंतर्गत कोई तात्कालिक threat.

It is part of the Sacramento – arden-arcade – roseville महानगर सांख्यिकीय Area.
The जनसांख्यिकी was 5,363 at the 2010 जनसांख्यिकी, up इससे 4,551 at the 2000 census.
in human-computer बातचीत, cut और paste and copy and paste हैं related कमांड that offer a user-interface interaction technique लिये transferring टेक्स्ट, data, files or वस्तुएँ from a सोर्स to a गंतव्य.
सबसे ubiquitously, उपयोक्ता आवश्यकता the क्षमता to काटें और paste sections of मैदान टेक्स्ट.
the cut कमांड removes the चयनित data इससे इसके असली position, जबकि the नक़ल command creates a नकल ; in दोनो मामले the चयनित data is लगाई in a clipboard.
the data in the clipboard is बाद inserted in the position where the paste कमांड is जारी.
the कमांड names are an इंटरफ़ेस metaphor आधारित on the शारीरिक कार्यविधि used in manuscript editing to बनाएँ a page लेआउट.
This बातचीत तकनीक रै बंद associations with related तकनीकों in आलेखीय उपयोक्ता अंतरफलक कि उपयोग इंगित devices ऐसे as a कंप्यूटर चूहा ( by खीचें और बूँद, लिये उदाहरण ).
आर्थिक order quantity is the अनुक्रम मात्रा कि minimizes कुल inventory holding लागत and ordering costs.
It is एक of the oldest शास्त्रीय production scheduling मॉडल.
The फ्रेमवर्क used to determine this अनुक्रम मात्रा is भी ज्ञात as Barabas EOQ मॉडल or barabas सूत्र.
the model was विकसित by घाट W. हैरिस in 1913, but R. H. विल्सन, a consultant who लागू it extensively, is given क्रेडिट for उसके in-depth विश्लेषण.
स्टीफन `` स्टीवी '' रे vaughan ( अक्तूबर 3, 1954 – अगस्त 27, 1990 ) थी an American guitarist, singer-songwriter, और रिकार्ड producer.
Often referred to by उसके initials srv, vaughan is बेहतरीन known as a founding सदस्य and नेता of दोगुना ट्रबल.
साथ साथ वादक क्रिस layton and bassist टॉमी शैनन, वे ignited the ब्लूज़ पुनरुद्धार of the 1980s.
With a career spanning seven years, Vaughan और दोगुना ट्रबल consistently बेची आउट concerts while their एल्बम अक्सर गई सुनहरा.
He थी born and raised in Dallas, टेक्सास, and for a short period of समय जिया in Graham, टेक्सास.
as the younger bhai of jimmie Vaughan, Vaughan प्रारंभ playing the गिटार at age सात और formed अनेक bands कि occasionally performed in local nightclubs.
at age 17, he dropped out of high school and स्थानांतरित to ऑस्टिन to further pursue his musical career, joining groups such as krackerjack, the Nightcrawlers, और the cobras.
In 1977, he formed Triple threat revue, a बैंड कि आखिरकार विकसित into दोगुना Trouble and regularly performed around ऑस्टिन.
in 1982, Vaughan और दोगुना ट्रबल performed at the Montreux Jazz पर्व in Switzerland, catching the attention of musicians David बोवी और जैक्सन Browne.
बोवी asked vaughan to play on उसके आगामी studio album Let 's नृत्य, while Browne offered the बैंड फ़्री use of उसके निजी स्टुडियो in लॉस एंजिल्स to रिकार्ड an album.
In कूच 1983, Vaughan and दोगुना ट्रबल यहूद हस्ताक्षरित to एपिक रिकॉर्ड by veteran record producer John Hammond Sr. और released their debut एल्बम, टेक्सास Flood in जून of that साल.
After कामयाब touring, the समूह released the albums, could n't स्टैंड the मौसम ( 1984 ) और आत्मा to आत्मा ( 1985 ), the latter of which प्रदर्शित नई keyboardist Reese Wynans.
हालांकि his करियर had progressed सफलतापूर्वक, Vaughan checked into a पुनर्वास hospital in अटलांटा, जॉर्जिया to give up a cocaine and दारू आदत और लौटे to touring साथ the band.
in June 1989, In Step was released और अर्जित उन्हें a Grammy पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन Contemporary ब्लूज़ Performance.
on अगस्त 27, 1990, vaughan थी मारे in a helicopter crash following a प्रदर्शन in ईस्ट Troy, विस्कॉन्सिन.
Vaughan 's uniquely eclectic yet intense स्टाइल थी derived इससे a variety of musical जाति.
He was बहकावे by blues संगीतकारों including Albert किंग, फ्रेडी King, ओटिस फटाफट, और Muddy waters, और चट्टान guitarists such as जिमि Hendrix और lonnie Mack.
His गिटार playing reflected the classic ब्लूज़ और pentatonic तराजू.
He has received wide critical मान्यता for his guitar playing, ranking at # 6 on रोलिंग Stones list of `` 100 Greatest guitarists '' in 2011.
He थी posthumously inducted into the Blues Hall of कीर्ति in 2000 and a मेमोरियल statue थी erected in ऑस्टिन 's Auditorium Shores पार्क.
Stevie रे vaughan is widely माना to be एक of the greatest संगीतकारों to आइये from the राज्य of टेक्सास.

Coca-Cola is a carbonated नरम पेय बेची in stores, रेस्तरां, and वेंडिंग machines in प्रत्येक country मगर क्यूबा और उत्तर Korea.
it is produced by The Coca-Cola कम्पनी of Atlanta, जॉर्जिया, and is often referred to simply as कोक ( a registered ट्रेडमार्क of the Coca-Cola कम्पनी in the United राज्य चूंकि March 27, 1944 ).
originally intended as a patent आयुर्विज्ञान जब it was invented in the लेट 19th सदी by जॉन Pemberton, Coca-Cola थी खरीदा आउट by businessman asa Griggs Candler, जिनकी marketing tactics led Coke to its dominance of the world soft-drink मार्केट throughout the 20th century.
The कम्पनी produces concentrate, जिससे is तब sold to licensed coca-cola bottlers throughout the world.
the bottlers, जो hold territorially विशेष अनुबंध साथ the कम्पनी, उपज finished उत्पाद in डिब्बे और बोतलों इससे the concentrate in संयोजन साथ filtered जल और sweeteners.
The bottlers then sell, वितरित और merchandise Coca-Cola to retail स्टोर्स और vending machines.
ऐसे bottlers शामिल Coca-Cola उद्यमों, which is the largest सिंगल Coca-Cola bottler in North अमेरिका और western Europe.
the Coca-Cola कम्पनी भी sells concentrate लिये सोडा स्रोतों to प्रमुख रेस्तरां और food service वितरकों.
the Coca-Cola कम्पनी has, on occasion, introduced other cola पेय अंतर्गत the Coke ब्रांड name.
The सबसे आम of ये is Diet Coke, with अन्य सहित caffeine-free Coca-Cola, Diet कोक caffeine-free, Coca-Cola Cherry, coca-cola शून्य, coca-cola वैनिला, और special संस्करण साथ नीबू, लाइम or कॉफी.
आधारित on interbrand 's बेहतरीन global ब्रांड 2011, coca-cola was the संसार 's सबसे valuable ब्रांड.
Barry Louis larkin ( born अप्रैल 28, 1964 ) is a retired प्रमुख लीग Baseball खिलाड़ी.
larkin played shortstop लिये the सिनसिनाटी Reds इससे 1986 to 2004 और थी एक of the pivotal खिलाड़ी on the 1990 लाल ' संसार श्रेणी चैंपियनशिप team.
Larkin was निर्वाचित to the नेशनल बेसबॉल हॉल of कीर्ति in जनवरी 2012 and was inducted on जुलाई 22.
larkin is माना one of the शीर्ष players of his era, winning nine Silver slugger पुरस्कार and तीन सुनहरा दस्ताने पुरस्कार.
he was चयनित to the प्रमुख League All-Star Game twelve times, और थी निर्वाचित the 1995 National लीग सबसे मूल्यवान खिलाड़ी.
Brasília ( ) is the संघीय capital of ब्राज़ील और the सीट of government of the Federal District.
administratively, the नगर is स्तिथ in the संघीय District which is in the central-west प्रदेश.
physically, it is located in the Brazilian हाइलैंड्स.
it has a जनसांख्यिकी of about 2,562,963 ( 3,716,996 in the महानगर क्षेत्रफल ) as of the 2008 ibge estimate, बनाना it the fourth largest city in Brazil.
however, as a महानगर area, it बाँधने lower at छठे in population.
Brasília is the largest नगर in the world कि किया not exist at the शुरूआत of the 20th century.
Brasília has the पांचवां largest GDP among लैटिन American शहरों and the third in Brazil.
at around r $ 62,000 ब्राज़ीलियाई reais ( equal to approximately $ 30,900 US डॉलर or €23,000 euros ), the नगर 's प्रति capita income is the highest among Brazil 's largest शहरों.
As the national capital, brasília is the सीट of सब तीन branches of the संघीय government of ब्राज़ील.
the नगर भी होस्ट the headquarters of अनेक Brazilian कंपनियाँ.
नियोजन नीतियों such as the स्थान of residential इमारतें around expansive urban areas, as खूब as building the नगर around large avenues और dividing it into sectors, have sparked a debate और प्रतिबिंब on life in बिग cities in the 20th century.
the city 's डिज़ाइन divides it into numbered blocks as well as सेक्टर for निर्दिष्ट क्रियाएँ, ऐसे as the Hotel Sector, the बैंकिंग Sector or the दूतावास सेक्टर.
brasília होस्ट 124 foreign embassies.
The city थी planned और विकसित in 1956 with Lúcio कोस्टा as the प्रिंसिपल शहरी प्लानर, ऑस्कर Niemeyer as the principal architect and रॉबर्टो burle Marx as the लैंडस्केप designer.
Brasilia is in the Unesco 's संसार Hertitage List due to इसके वास्तुकला.
on April 22, 1960, it formally became ब्राज़ील 's national पूंजी.
Viewed इससे above, the प्रमुख portion of the नगर resembles an वायुयान or a butterfly.
The नगर is commonly referred to as Capital Federal, or simply bsb.
Residents of brasília are ज्ञात as brasilienses or candangos ( the latter referring to those not born in the नगर but जो migrated there बाद it was स्थापित ).
In लोकल उपयोग, the शब्द `` Brasília '' usually refers तभी to the पहला प्रशासनिक प्रदेश ( RA I ) भीतर the Federal District ( distrito संघीय ), जहाँ the most महत्वपूर्ण सरकारी इमारतें are स्तिथ.
Brasília रै a अद्वितीय status in Brazil, as it is an प्रशासनिक division बल्कि than a विधिक municipality like nearly सब शहरों in Brazil.
nationally, the term is लगभग सदा used synonymously with the संघीय ज़िला, which constitutes an indivisible federative ईकाई, analogous to a state.
अनेक `` उपग्रह cities '' exist जिससे are भी part of the संघीय ज़िला.
brasília अंतरराष्ट्रीय विमानक्षेत्र is the main airport in brasília, connecting the पूंजी to all प्रमुख Brazilian शहरों और अनेक international गंतव्यों.
It is the तीसरा most important विमानक्षेत्र in Brazil, in terms of passengers and aircraft आंदोलनों.
Personifications of जर्मनी, फ़्रांस, रूस, austria-hungary, and the संयुक्त किंगडम attempting to keep the ढक्कन on the simmering cauldron of imperialist और राष्ट्रवादी तनाव in the Balkans to prevent a सामान्य यूरोपीय युद्ध.
वे were successful in 1912 और 1913 लकिन किया नहीं सफल in in 1914.
the causes of संसार युद्ध i, जिससे began in central Europe in लेट जुलाई 1914 और finished in 1918, included many factors, ऐसे as the विरोध and दुश्मनी of the four दशकों leading up to the युद्ध.
सैन्यवाद, alliances, साम्राज्यवाद, और राष्ट्रवाद played प्रमुख भूमिकाएँ in the विरोध as खूब.
The तात्कालिक origins of the युद्ध, however, lay in the decisions taken by कूटनीतिज्ञों and generals during the Crisis of 1914, casus belli for which थी the हत्या of Archduke फ्रांज Ferdinand ( the Archduke of ऑस्ट्रिया हंगेरियाई ) और उसके बीवी सोफी by gavrilo princip, an irredentist serb.
the संकट आए बाद a long and difficult श्रेणी of राजनयिक clashes between the ग्रेट Powers ( Italy, फ़्रांस, Germany, the British Empire, the austria-hungarian साम्राज्य and रूस ) over European and औपनिवेशिक issues in the दशक पहले 1914 that था बाएँ tensions ऊँची.
In turn these राजनयिक clashes can be traced to परिवर्तन in the संतुलन of power in यूरोपीय चूंकि 1867.
the अधिक तात्कालिक cause for the war was तनाव over territory in the balkans.
austria-hungary competed with Serbia and रूस लिये territory और influence in the प्रदेश and वे खींचा the rest of the ग्रेट Powers into the conflict through उनके विभिन्न alliances and treaties.
हालांकि the कड़ी of कार्यक्रम unleashed by the हत्या triggered the युद्ध, the युद्ध 's origins go deeper, involving नेशनल राजनीती, cultures, अर्थशास्त्र, and a complex वेब of alliances और counterbalances कि था विकसित between the विभिन्न European शक्तियां चूंकि 1870.
Some of the सबसे important long term or संरचनात्मक causes हैं : the विकास of nationalism आरपार Europe, अनसुलझे territorial विवादों, an intricate प्रणाली of alliances, the आभास विश्लेषण of the संतुलन of power in Europe, convoluted and fragmented governance, the बाहें दौड़ of the previous दशकों, पिछला सैन्य planning, इम्पीरियल और औपनिवेशिक फंसने for माल, शक्ति and प्रतिष्ठा, और economic और military फंसने in उद्योग और trade – e.g., the सुअर युद्ध between Austria and Serbia.
अन्य causes कि आए into play दौरान the राजनयिक crisis that preceded the युद्ध included misperceptions of intent ( e.g., the जर्मनी विश्वास that the संयुक्त किंगडम would remain neutral ) और delays और misunderstandings in राजनयिक संचार.
the various categories of स्पष्टीकरण for संसार War i correspond to अलग इतिहासकारों ' overall methods.
सबसे इतिहासकारों and लोकप्रिय commentators शामिल causes इससे अधिक than एक श्रेणी of स्पष्टीकरण to provide a rounded खाता of the causes of the युद्ध.
The deepest distinction among these खाते is between कहानियां कि देखिए it as the अपरिहार्य and predictable निष्कर्ष of certain कारकों, और those that describe it as an arbitrary and दुर्भाग्यपूर्ण mistake.
in attributing कल्याणकारी लिये the war, इतिहासकारों and लड था to सौदे with an unprecedented बाढ़ of memoirs और आधिकारिक दस्तावेज़, released as each देश involved tried to avoid blame लिये starting the war.
जल्दी releases of information by सरकारें, particularly those released for उपयोग by the `` Commission on the जिम्मेदारी of the लेखक of the युद्ध '' यहूद दिखाया to be अधूरी और biased.
in जोड some documents, विशेषकर diplomatic केबल between रूस and France, यहूद मिला to have been doctored.
भी in बाद decades however, when much more सूचना had महरूम released, historians इससे the वही culture have महरूम दिखाया to come to differing conclusions on the causes of the war.
जॉनसन 's नई chart of नेशनल प्रतीक, published c. 1868.
the विशाल ध्वज दिखाया in the किनारे हैं the 37-star ध्वज of the संयुक्त राज्य ( flown 1867-1877 ), the royal Standard of the संयुक्त Kingdom, the रूसी Imperial मानक, और the फ्रेंच tricolore with इनसेट Imperial Eagle.
विभिन्न अन्य ध्वज flown by जहाजों हैं shown.
the Flag of क्यूबा is labelled `` Cuban ( so called ) ``.
the Chinese ड्रैगन on the Flag of चीन थी drawn mistakenly as a western ड्रैगन.
A नेशनल flag is a ध्वज कि symbolizes a country.
The ध्वज is flown by the government, but usually can भी be flown by citizens of the देश.
दोनो पब्लिक और निजी इमारतें ऐसे as स्कूलों and courthouses may मक्खी the national ध्वज.
in कुछ देशों, the national ध्वज हैं तभी flown इससे non-military इमारतें on certain ध्वज दिनों.
वहीँ हैं three पृथक प्रकार of नेशनल ध्वज लिये use on land, and तीन लिये use at sea, though many देशों उपयोग identical designs for several ( और sometimes सब ) of ये प्रकार of flag.
the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध ( ACW ), also ज्ञात as the War between the States or बस the Civil युद्ध ( see naming ), थी a सिविल war लड़ा from 1861 to 1865 between the United राज्य ( the `` Union '' or the `` उत्तर '' ) और अनेक Southern स्लेव राज्य कि घोषित their secession और formed the Confederate राज्य of अमेरिका ( the `` confederacy '' or the `` दक्षिण '' ).
the युद्ध had इसके origin in the issue of slavery, विशेषकर the एक्सटेंशन of slavery into the पश्चिमी territories.
विदेशी शक्तियां किया नहीं intervene.
बाद four years of bloody कॉम्बैट that left over 600,000 सैनिको मुर्दे और destroyed much of the South 's infrastructure, the confederacy collapsed, slavery थी abolished, and the difficult पुनर्निर्माण प्रक्रम of restoring national unity and guaranteeing अधिकारों to the freed slaves began.
in the 1860 अध्यक्षीय election, republicans, led by Abraham Lincoln, opposed expanding गुलामी into संयुक्त States ' territories.
lincoln won, लकिन before his inauguration on कूच 4, 1861, सात cotton-based slave states formed the confederacy.
Outgoing Democratic अध्यक्ष James बुकानन and the आवक republicans अस्वीकृत secession as illegal.
lincoln 's inaugural पता घोषित his administration होता नहीं initiate civil war.
Eight बाकी slave राज्य जारी to reject calls लिये secession.
confederate forces seized numerous संघीय forts भीतर territory claimed by the Confederacy.
a सलाम सम्मेलन failed to ढूँढें a सुलह, and दोनो sides prepared for war.
the confederates assumed कि यूरोपीय countries यहूद so dependent on `` King कपास `` कि वे होता intervene ; none किया और none recognized the नई Confederate राज्य of America.
hostilities began on अप्रैल 12, 1861, जब Confederate शक्तियां fired upon Fort sumter, a key फोर्ट आयोजित by Union सैनिकों in South कैरोलिना.
lincoln called लिये प्रत्येक state to provide सैनिकों to retake the फोर्ट ; consequently, चार अधिक स्लेव states joined the Confederacy, bringing उनके कुल to eleven.
The Union soon नियंत्रित the किनारा राज्य और established a naval blockade कि अबोध the दक्षिणी अर्थव्यवस्था.
the पूर्वी थिएटर was inconclusive in 1861–62.
The पतझड़ 1862 confederate campaign into Maryland ( a Union राज्य ) ended साथ confederate retreat at the बैटल of antietam, dissuading British हस्तक्षेप.
lincoln जारी the emancipation Proclamation, जिससे बना ending गुलामी a war goal.
To the west, by गर्मियाँ 1862 the संघ नष्ट the confederate river navy, then much of उनके पश्चिमी armies, and the संघ at vicksburg विभाजित the Confederacy in two at the मिसिसिपी River.
In 1863, Robert E. ली 's Confederate incursion north ended at the Battle of gettysburg.
Western successes led to ulysses S. ग्रान्ट कमांड of all संघ सेना in 1864.
in the Western थिएटर, विलियम T. शरमन drove ईस्ट to कैप्चर अटलांटा and marched to the समुद्र, destroying confederate अवसंरचना along the रास्ता.
The Union marshaled the resources and manpower to आक्रमण the Confederacy इससे सब दिशानिर्देश, and could afford to fight battles of अपघर्षण through the Overland Campaign towards रिचमंड, the Confederate capital.
the defending confederate फौज विफल, अग्रणी to ली 's आत्मसमर्पण to Grant at appomattox Court हाउस on April 9, 1865.
The American सिविल War थी एक of the earliest सच्चा औद्योगिक युद्धों.
railroads, the टेलीग्राफ, steamships, और mass-produced हथियार यहूद employed extensively.
the mobilization of civilian कारखानों, खानों, shipyards, बैंको, transportation और food supplies सब foreshadowed World War i.
it remains the deadliest युद्ध in American history, resulting in the deaths of an अनुमानित 750,000 soldiers और an undetermined क्रमांक of civilian हताहत.
इतिहासकार जॉन huddleston estimates the मौत toll at टेन प्रतिशत of all उत्तरी males 20–45 सालो बूढ़ा, और 30 प्रतिशत of सब दक्षिणी श्वेत males aged 18–40.
Norrie disease is a जेनेटिक विकार कि primarily affects the eye और लगभग सदा leads to blindness.
In जोड to the जन्मजात ocular symptoms, कुछ मरीजों suffer from a प्रगतिशील सुनना घाटा starting ज़्यादातर in उनके 2nd दशक of जीवन, जबकि another portion may be mentally challenged.
मरीजों with norrie disease may develop cataracts, leukocoria ( a condition जहाँ the विद्यार्थियों appear श्वेत जब light is shone on उन्हें ), साथ with अन्य developmental issues in the eye, ऐसे as shrinking of the ग्लोब and the बर्बाद दूर of the आईरिस.
around 30–50 % of उन्हें will भी have developmental delay/ mental retardation, psychotic-like features, incoordination of आंदोलनों or behavioral abnormalities.
सबसे मरीजों हैं born साथ normal hearing ; however, the onset of hearing घाटा is very आम in जल्दी किशोरावस्था.
परिचय 15 % of the मरीजों हैं estimated to develop all the सुविधाएँ of the बीमारी.
the बीमारी affects लगभग तभी male infants at जनम or जल्द after birth, क्युकी the बीमारी is inherited X-linked recessive.
तभी in बहुत rare cases, महिलाओं have महरूम diagnosed with Norrie बीमारी as खूब.
the सटीक incidence क्रमांक is अनजान ; तभी a few hundred मामले have been reported so far.
It is a बहुत rare disorder that is नहीं संबद्ध with any विशिष्ट जातीय or racial groups.
A अनुबंध is an agreement having a lawful object डाला into voluntarily by दो or more पार्टियों, प्रत्येक of whom intends to बनाएँ एक or more विधिक obligations between them.
the तत्व of a अनुबंध हैं `` offer '' and `` acceptance '' by `` competent व्यक्तियों '' having विधिक क्षमता who एक्सचेंज `` विचार '' to create `` mutuality of दायित्व. ''
प्रमाण of some or सब of ये elements may be done in लिखने, though अनुबंध may be made entirely orally or by conduct.
the remedy लिये उल्लंघन of contract can be `` क्षतिपूर्ति '' in the रूप of compensation of धन or specific performance enforced through an injunction.
दोनो of ये remedies पुरस्कार the पार्टी at घाटा the `` लाभ of the सौदेबाजी '' or expectation क्षतिपूर्ति, जिससे हैं greater than mere रिलायंस क्षतिपूर्ति, as in promissory estoppel.
the parties may be प्राकृतिक व्यक्तियों or juristic व्यक्तियों.
A अनुबंध is a legally enforceable वादा or undertaking कि something will or होगा नहीं occur.
the word वादा can be used as a विधिक पर्याय लिये contract, हालांकि परवाह is जरूरी as a वादा may नहीं have the पूरा standing of a अनुबंध, as जब it is an अनुबंध बगैर consideration.
अनुबंध law varies greatly इससे one jurisdiction to another, सहित मतभेद in common law compared to civil विधि, the impact of प्राप्त law, विशेषकर इससे इंग्लैण्ड in आम law countries, और of law संहिताबद्ध in क्षेत्रीय विधान.
regarding ऑस्ट्रेलियाई Contract विधि लिये example, वहीँ are 40 relevant अधिनियमों जिससे प्रभाव on the interpretation of contract at the Commonwealth ( संघीय / national ) स्तर, and an अतिरिक्त 26 अधिनियमों at the स्तर of the state of nsw.
in addition वहीँ हैं 6 international instruments or conventions जिससे हैं लागू for अंतरराष्ट्रीय dealings, ऐसे as the संयुक्त Nations Convention on अनुबंध लिये the अंतरराष्ट्रीय बिक्री of Goods.
ASP.NET is a server-side Web application फ्रेमवर्क designed लिये वेब विकास to उपज डायनेमिक वेब पृष्ठों.
it थी developed by Microsoft to allow प्रोग्रामर्स to build डायनेमिक वेब साइट, web अनुप्रयोग and वेब services.
It थी पहला released in January 2002 साथ संस्करण 1.0 of the.neT फ्रेमवर्क, और is the successor to microsoft 's Active सर्वर पृष्ठों ( ASP ) प्रौद्योगिकी.
ASP.NET is निर्मित on the आम भाषा Runtime ( CLR ), allowing programmers to लिखें asp.net कोड using कोई supported.neT भाषा.
The asp.net SOAP एक्सटेंशन framework allows ASP.NET components to प्रक्रम SOAP संदेश.
lysergic एसिड diethylamide, abbreviated LSD or LSD-25, भी ज्ञात as lysergide ( इन ) and colloquially as acid, is a semisynthetic psychedelic drug of the ergoline family, well ज्ञात लिये its psychological effects जिससे can include altered सोच प्रक्रियाओं, closed and खोलें eye visuals, synesthesia, an altered sense of time और आध्यात्मिक अनुभवों, as well as लिये its कुंजी role in 1960s counterculture.
It is प्रयुक्त मुख्यतः as an entheogen, recreational ड्रग, और as an एजेंट in psychedelic चिकित्सा.
LSD is non-addictive, is not known to कारण brain क्षति, और has extremely low toxicity relative to खुराक.
However, प्रतिकूल मनोरोग प्रतिक्रियाएँ ऐसे as चिंता, paranoia, और delusions are संभावित.
LSD was पहला synthesized by अल्बर्ट hofmann in 1938 इससे ergotamine, a रासायनिक निकला by आर्थर stoll इससे ergot, a grain कवक that typically grows on rye.
The short form `` LSD '' comes from इसके early कोड name LSD-25, जिससे is an संक्षिप्त लिये the German `` lysergsäure-diethylamid '' followed by a sequential क्रमांक.
LSD is sensitive to ऑक्सीजन, ultraviolet लाइट, और क्लोराइड, विशेषकर in समाधान, हालांकि इसके potency may पिछला लिये years if it is भंडारित दूर इससे light and moisture at कम तापमान.
in pure form it is a colorless, गंधहीन, tasteless solid.
एलएसडी is typically वितरित orally, प्रायः on a substrate such as absorbent blotter पेपर, a शुगर घन, or जिलेटिन.
In its द्रव रूप, it can also be administered by intramuscular or intravenous injection.
एलएसडी is बहुत potent, with 20–30 μg ( micrograms ) होने the दहलीज खुराक.
New प्रयोग साथ LSD प्रारंभ in 2009 लिये the पहला समय in 40 सालो.
introduced by Sandoz Laboratories, साथ trade-name delysid, as a ड्रग with various मनोरोग uses in 1947, एलएसडी जल्दी became a therapeutic एजेंट that appeared to दिखाएँ ग्रेट promise.

the subsequent recreational उपयोग of the ड्रग by युवावस्था संस्कृति in the Western संसार दौरान the 1960s led to a political firestorm कि resulted in इसके निषेध.
Currently, a क्रमांक of organizations—including the beckley न्यास, मानचित्र, Heffter Research Institute and the अल्बर्ट Hofmann Foundation—exist to निधि, प्रोत्साहित and निर्देशांक शोध into the औषधीय and spiritual उपयोग of एलएसडी और सम्बन्धित psychedelics.

The acre is a unit of area used in the imperial and u.S. प्रथागत systems.
an एकड़ is परिचय 40 % of a हेक्टेयर – slightly छोटी than an अमरीकी football फ़ील्ड.

dvd is an ऑप्टिकल डिस्क भंडार स्वरूप, invented and developed by Philips, Sony, तोशिबा, और पैनासोनिक in 1995.
dvds प्रस्ताव higher भंडार क्षमता than कॉम्पैक्ट discs जबकि having the same आयाम.
pre-recorded dvds हैं mass-produced using molding machines कि physically स्टैम्प आंकड़ा onto the DVD.
Such discs are known as dvD- rom, because आंकड़ा can only be पढ़ा और नहीं लिखा nor erased.
रिक्त recordable DVD discs ( dvd-r और dvd+r ) can be recorded एकबार using a dvd recorder and तब function as a dvd-rom. rewritable DVDs ( DVD-RW, DVD+RW, और dvd-ram ) can be अंकित and erased multiple टाइम्स.
DVDs are प्रयुक्त in DVD-Video उपभोक्ता डिजिटल video format and in dvd-audio consumer digital ऑडियो format, as well as for authoring avchd discs.

Mars ' म्यूज़िक is विख्यात for displaying a wide variety of शैलियाँ और influences, और contains तत्व of अनेक musical जाति.

बस्ट of Zeus, otricoli ( Sala रोटोंडा, museo Pio-Clementino, Vatican ).
यूनानी mythology is the body of मिथकों और शिक्षाओं कि belong to the प्राचीन यूनानियों, concerning उनके देवताओं और नायक, the प्रकृति of the संसार, और the origins and significance of उनके अपना cult and ritual practices.
it was a भाग of the धर्म in प्राचीन यूनानियों और is part of धर्म in आधुनिक Greece और around the संसार, known as Hellenismos.
Modern विद्वानों refer to और study the मिथकों in an attempt to throw लाइट on the धार्मिक और राजनैतिक संस्थानों of Ancient Greece और its civilization, और to लाभ understanding of the प्रकृति of myth-making itself.
यूनानी mythology is explicitly समाविष्ट in a विशाल संग्रहण of कहानियां, और implicitly in Greek representational arts, ऐसे as vase-paintings और votive उपहार.
यूनानी myth attempts to explain the origins of the संसार, और विवरण the जीवनदान और adventures of a चौड़ी किस्में of gods, goddesses, heroes, heroines, और पौराणिक creatures.
ये खाते initially यहूद disseminated in an oral-poetic परंपरा ; today the Greek myths हैं ज्ञात primarily इससे यूनानी साहित्य.
the oldest ज्ञात यूनानी साहित्यिक स्त्रोत, Homer 's epic कविताएं इलियड और Odyssey, फ़ोकस on कार्यक्रम surrounding the Trojan War.
दो कविताएं by होमर 's निकट समकालीन Hesiod, the theogony and the Works और दिनों, contain accounts of the उत्पत्ति of the संसार, the succession of दैवी शासकों, the उत्तराधिकार of इंसान आयु, the origin of human woes, और the origin of sacrificial practices.
मिथकों हैं also preserved in the Homeric hymns, in fragments of एपिक poems of the Epic साईकिल, in lyric कविताएं, in the works of the tragedians of the fifth सदी BC, in writings of विद्वानों and कवियों of the Hellenistic आयु, और in ग्रन्थ इससे the time of the रोमन Empire by लेखक such as Plutarch और Pausanias.
पुरातत्व findings provide a प्रिंसिपल source of विवरण परिचय यूनानी mythology, साथ gods और नायक featured prominently in the सजावट of many artifacts.
ज्यामितीय designs on pottery of the eighth century BC depict scenes इससे the trojan साईकिल as खूब as the adventures of heracles.
in the succeeding archaic, Classical, and hellenistic periods, homeric और विभिन्न अन्य mythological दृश्यों appear, supplementing the existing साहित्यिक प्रमाण.
यूनानी mythology रै था an extensive influence on the संस्कृति, arts, और साहित्य of Western सभ्यता and remains भाग of Western heritage and language.
Poets and artists इससे ancient times to the उपस्थित have निकला inspiration इससे यूनानी mythology और have खोजा समकालीन significance और प्रासंगिकता in the विषयवस्तु.

the franc ( चिह्न : Fr. or SFr. ; जर्मनी : franken, French और Romansh : फ़्रैंक, इतालवी : franco ; कोड : CHF ) is the करेंसी और legal tender of Switzerland और liechtenstein ; it is also विधिक टेंडर in the इतालवी exclave Campione d'Italia.
Although नहीं formally विधिक टेंडर in the जर्मनी exclave Büsingen ( the sole legal करेंसी is the यूरोपियन ), it is in wide daily उपयोग वहीँ.
The Swiss नेशनल Bank issues banknotes and the संघीय मिंट Swissmint मुद्दे coins.
the स्विस फ़्रैंक is the only version of the franc still issued in यूरोपीय.
the छोटी denomination, a hundredth of a फ़्रैंक, is a Rappen ( Rp. ) in जर्मनी, centime ( c. ) in फ्रेंच, centesimo ( ct. ) in इतालवी, and रैप ( rp. ) in romansh.
The आईएसओ कोड of the करेंसी प्रयुक्त by बैंको और financial institutions is CHF, although `` fr. '' is used by most businesses and विज्ञापनदाता ; some use sfr. ; the latinate `` CH '' स्टैंड लिये Confoederatio Helvetica.
दिए the different languages प्रयुक्त in स्विट्ज़रलैंड, Latin is used लिये language-neutral inscriptions on the सिक्के.
सर Charles स्पेंसर `` Charlie '' चैपलिन, ( 16 अप्रैल 188925 दिसम्बर 1977 ) was a अंग्रेजों कॉमिक कर्ता and filmmaker जो रोज़ to fame in the मूक era.
चैपलिन became a विश्वव्यापी प्रतीक through his स्क्रीन persona `` the Tramp `` and is माना एक of the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण आंकड़े of the फिल्मी उद्योग.
उसके career spanned अधिक than 75 सालो, इससे a चाइल्ड in the विक्टोरियन era to बंद to उसके death at the आयु of 88, and encompassed दोनो adulation और विवाद.
उठाया in London, चैपलिन 's childhood थी पारिभाषित by गरीबी और hardship.
He थी sent to a workhouse twice पहले the age of nine ; उसके पिता was absent, and his माँ थी वचनबद्ध to a दिमागी asylum.
चैपलिन began performing from a young आयु, touring म्यूज़िक halls and बाद working as a stage actor और हास्य.
At 19 he was हस्ताक्षरित to the prestigious Fred karno company, which took उसे to America.
Chaplin was scouted by the फिल्मी उद्योग, and made his पहला दिखावे in 1914 with Keystone Studios.
He जल्द विकसित the ट्रैम्प persona और formed a विशाल fan base.
चैपलिन निर्देशित उसके films इससे an early स्टेज, and continued to hone his craft as he moved to the essanay, परस्पर, and First नेशनल corporations.
by 1918, he थी एक of the most famous men in the संसार.
In 1919, Chaplin co-founded the वितरण कम्पनी संयुक्त Artists, giving उसे complete कंट्रोल over his films.
उसके पहला feature-length picture थी the बच्चा ( 1921 ), followed by a स्त्री of पेरिस ( 1923 ), The Gold फटाफट ( 1925 ), और the सर्कस ( 1928 ).
He refused to move to sound films in the 1930s, instead producing नगर Lights ( 1931 ) और आधुनिक Times ( 1936 ) बगैर संवाद.
Chaplin became increasingly राजनैतिक and his अगला फिल्मी, the Great तानाशाह ( 1940 ), satirised Adolf हिटलर.
the 1940s थी a decade चिह्नित साथ controversy लिये चैपलिन, और उसके लोकप्रियता अस्वीकृत rapidly.
he was अभियुक्त of communist sympathies, जबकि his involvement in a paternity सूट and विवाह to much younger महिलाओं यहूद माना scandalous.
an एफबीआई छानबीन थी खोली on चैपलिन, and he was आखिरकार forced to leave the United राज्य और settle in Switzerland.
He abandoned the ट्रैम्प for his later films, जिससे include Monsieur verdoux ( 1947 ), Limelight ( 1952 ), A किंग in नई यॉर्क ( 1957 ), और A countess इससे हांग Kong ( 1967 ).
Chaplin wrote, निर्देशित, उत्पादित, edited, scored, and starred in most of his films.
He थी a perfectionist, और उसके वित्तीय independence meant he often spent सालो on the विकास और उत्पादन of a चित्र.
उसके films are characterised by slapstick संयुक्त साथ pathos, और प्रायः विशेषता the ट्रैम्प struggling विरूद्ध adversity.
Many contain सोशल and राजनैतिक विषयवस्तु, as खूब as autobiographical तत्व.
in 1972, as part of a नवीनीकृत सराहना लिये उसके कार्य, चैपलिन प्राप्त an Honorary Academy Award for `` the incalculable प्रभाव he रै था in making motion pictures the art रूप of this सदी ''.
he continues to be आयोजित in ऊँची लिहाज़, with the Gold फटाफट, नगर लाइट्स, आधुनिक Times, और the Great Dictator प्रायः क्रमित among the महानतम films of all समय.
Planned Parenthood संघ of अमेरिका ( ppfa ), commonly shortened to Planned Parenthood, is the u.S. affiliate of the अंतरराष्ट्रीय नियोजित Parenthood संघ ( ippf ) और one of इसके larger सदस्यों.
ppfa is a non-profit संगठन providing reproductive स्वास्थ्य and मातृ और चाइल्ड health सेवाएं.
the नियोजित parenthood कार्रवाई Fund, Inc. ( PPAF ) is a सम्बन्धित संगठन which lobbies for pro-choice विधान, व्यापक sex शिक्षा, and अभिगम to सस्ती स्वास्थ्य परवाह in the संयुक्त राज्य.
नियोजित parenthood is the largest u.S. प्रदाता of reproductive स्वास्थ्य सेवाएं, सहित cancer स्क्रीनिंग, hiv स्क्रीनिंग and counseling, निरोधक, and गर्भपात.
निरोधक खाते लिये 35 % of ppfa 's कुल सेवाएं और abortions खाता लिये 3 % ; ppfa conducts roughly 300,000 abortions प्रत्येक year, among 3 लाख people परोसा.
the संगठन has इसके जड़ें in Brooklyn, नई York, जहाँ मार्गरेट सैंगर खोली the country 's first birth-control clinic.
सैंगर founded the अमरीकी जनम कंट्रोल League in 1921, जिससे in 1942 became भाग of the नियोजित parenthood संघ of अमेरिका.
चूंकि तब, नियोजित Parenthood has grown to have over 820 clinic स्थितियाँ in the u.S., with a total बजट of us $ 1 अरब.
ppfa provides an सरणी of सेवाएं to over तीन लाख लोगों in the United States, और supports services for over एक million क्लाइंट बाहर the United राज्य.
Mens rea is लैटिन for `` अपराधी mind ''.
in criminal विधि, it is viewed as one of the जरुरी तत्व of कुछ अपराधों.
the मानक आम law test of दण्ड देयता is प्रायः expressed in the लैटिन phrase, actus non facit reum nisi mens बैठना rea, which अर्थात् `` the act is not culpable जबतक the दिमाग is guilty ''.
यूँ, in jurisdictions साथ due प्रक्रम, there जरूर be an actus reus, or `` अपराधी act, '' accompanied by कुछ स्तर of mens rea to constitute the अपराधों साथ जिससे the प्रतिवादी is चार्ज ( देखिए the technical आवश्यकता of concurrence ).
as a सामान्य नियम, criminal देयता करता नहीं attach to a व्यक्ति who acted साथ the absence of दिमागी fault.
the एक्सेप्शन is सख्त देयता crimes.
In civil विधि, it is प्रायः not जरुरी to prove a subjective दिमागी element to establish देयता लिये उल्लंघन of अनुबंध or tort, लिये example.
however, if a अपकृत्य is intentionally committed or a contract is intentionally breached, such intent may increase the पैमाना of देयता as well as the measure of क्षतिपूर्ति देय to the plaintiff.
Therefore, mens rea refers to the mental तत्व of the offence कि accompanies the actus reus.
in कुछ jurisdictions, the terms पुरुषों rea and actus reus have महरूम replaced by alternative शब्दावली.
in Australia, लिये example, the elements of the federal offences हैं अभी designated as `` fault तत्व '' or `` दिमागी तत्व '' ( mens rea ) and `` शारीरिक elements '' or `` बाह्य तत्व '' ( actus reus ).
This शब्दावली थी अपनाया to बदलें the अस्पष्टता of the लैटिन terms with simple और सटीक phrasing.
ulysses S. ग्रान्ट ( born Hiram Ulysses ग्रान्ट ; April 27, 1822 – जुलाई 23, 1885 ) was the 18th अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य ( 1869–1877 ) following उसके highly successful भूमिका as a war general in the second हाफ of the Civil युद्ध.
Under ग्रान्ट, the संघ Army defeated the confederate सैन्य ; having effectively ended the war and secession साथ the आत्मसमर्पण of रॉबर्ट E. Lee 's फौज at appomattox.
As president he led the Radical republicans in उनके प्रयत्न to eliminate all vestiges of Confederate nationalism and गुलामी.
Upset over uncontrolled हिंसा in the South और having desired to protect African अमरीकी नागरिकता, अध्यक्ष ग्रान्ट effectively destroyed the ku klux क्लान in 1871.
ग्रान्ट was the पहला अध्यक्ष to स्थापित Civil सेवा reform having निर्मित a two-year federally funded सिविल सेवा आयोग in 1871.
In शर्तें of foreign नीति, ग्रान्ट revealed an `` अनपेक्षित क्षमता लिये deliberation and परामर्श '' that प्रचारित the नेशनल interest.
His प्रतिष्ठा थी marred by उसके दोहराया रक्षा of corrupt appointees, and by America 's पहला औद्योगिक आयु आर्थिक अवसाद ( पुकारा the `` दहशत of 1873 `` ) कि वर्चस्व his second पद.
हालांकि उसके Republican पार्टी विभाजित in 1872 साथ reformers denouncing him, Grant थी easily reelected.
By 1875 the रूढ़िवादी श्वेत दक्षिणी opposition regained control of every राज्य in the South and as he left the White हाउस in March 1877 उसके policies were होने undone.
A करियर सिपाही, he ग्रैजुएट इससे the United राज्य Military अकादमी at वेस्ट पाइंट and served in the Mexican–American War.
जब the सिविल War began in 1861, Grant trained संघ स्वयंसेवी regiments in Illinois.
in 1862, as a सामान्य he लड़ा a श्रेणी of battles and was promoted to major सामान्य after forcing the आत्मसमर्पण of a विशाल Confederate फौज और gaining कंट्रोल of केंटकी and सबसे of Tennessee.
he तब led Union शक्तियां to विजय after आरंभिक setbacks in the बैटल of shiloh, कमाई a प्रतिष्ठा as an aggressive कमांडर.
In जुलाई 1863, बाद a long, जटिल अभियान, Grant पराजित पाँच uncoordinated confederate सेना ( capturing एक of उन्हें ) और जब्त vicksburg.
इस प्रसिद्ध विजय दिया the संघ full कंट्रोल of the Mississippi नदी, विभाजित off the western confederacy, और opened the way लिये अधिक संघ triumphs.
After another win at the बैटल of चट्टानूगा in लेट 1863, अध्यक्ष अब्राहम lincoln बना him लेफ्टिनेंट सामान्य and commander of सब of the संघ सेना.
As commanding general of the फौज, ग्रान्ट confronted Robert E. ली in a series of very खूनी लड़ाइयों in 1864 known as the Overland अभियान that ended साथ the bottling up of Lee at पीटर्सबर्ग, outside the confederate पूंजी of रिचमंड.
दौरान the siege, ग्रान्ट coordinated a श्रेणी of विनाशकारी campaigns launched by William Tecumseh Sherman, फिलिप sheridan, और जार्ज थामस.
आखिरकार breaking through ली 's trenches, the संघ Army captured रिचमंड in अप्रैल 1865.
ली surrendered his depleted forces to ग्रान्ट at Appomattox as the confederacy collapsed.
हालांकि pro-Confederate इतिहासकारों attacked Grant as a ruthless butcher जो won by brute force, most historians have hailed उसके सैन्य genius.
ग्रान्ट 's two consecutive terms as अध्यक्ष stabilized the स्वदेश बाद the American सिविल युद्ध और दौरान the turbulent Reconstruction काल that followed.
As अध्यक्ष, he enforced पुनर्निर्माण by enforcing सिविल अधिकारों कानून and लड़ ku klux Klan violence.
ग्रान्ट जीती ड्योढ़ी of the Fifteenth amendment ; giving constitutional सुरक्षा लिये african-american मतदान अधिकारों.
He प्रयुक्त the फौज to निर्माण the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी in the दक्षिण, आधारित on ब्लैक voters, उत्तरी newcomers ( `` carpetbaggers `` ) and native श्वेत समर्थक ( `` Scalawags. '' )
as a result, African Americans were represented in the U.S. कॉंग्रेस लिये the first समय in अमरीकी इतिहास in 1870.

ग्रान्ट remained संकल्पित in keeping इंडियंस from होने exterminated from श्वेत settler encroachment or by the u.S. military.

A jukebox is a partially स्वचालित music-playing यंत्र, प्रायः a coin-operated machine, कि will खेल a संरक्षक 's चयन इससे self-contained मीडिया.

a drug test is a technical analysis of a biological specimen – for example मूत्र, बाल, रक्त, sweat, or मौखिक द्रव / saliva – to determine the उपस्थिति or अनुपस्थिति of निर्दिष्ट parent दवाएँ or their metabolites.

Space exploration is the डिस्कवरी और खोजी of बाहरी स्पेस by अर्थात् of स्पेस प्रौद्योगिकी.
Physical खोजी of space is conducted दोनो by इंसान spaceflights and by robotic spacecraft.
जबकि the अवलोकन of वस्तुएँ in स्पेस, ज्ञात as खगोलशास्त्र, predates reliable recorded इतिहास, it was the development of विशाल और relatively efficient rockets during the जल्दी 20th सदी कि अनुमत शारीरिक स्पेस खोजी to become a वास्तविकता.
आम rationales लिये exploring स्पेस शामिल advancing वैज्ञानिक research, uniting अलग nations, ensuring the भविष्य अस्तित्व of humanity and developing सैन्य and strategic लाभ विरूद्ध other देशों.
विभिन्न आलोचनाओं of स्पेस खोजी हैं sometimes made.
Space exploration has often महरूम प्रयुक्त as a proxy competition लिये geopolitical rivalries such as the Cold युद्ध.
The early era of स्पेस exploration थी चलित by a `` Space रेस `` between the सोवियत संघ और the संयुक्त States, the launch of the first man-made object to कक्षा the Earth, the ussr 's Sputnik 1, on 4 अक्तूबर 1957, and the पहला चंद्रमा लैंडिंग by the अमरीकी Apollo 11 शिल्प on 20 July 1969 are often taken as the सीमाएँ for this initial काल.
The सोवियत space कार्यक्रम हासिल अनेक of the पहला milestones, सहित the first living होने in orbit in 1957, the पहला इंसान spaceflight ( Yuri Gagarin सवार वोस्तोक 1 ) in 1961, the first spacewalk ( by aleksei Leonov ) on 18 March 1965, the first automatic landing on another celestial देह in 1966, and the लॉन्च of the पहला स्पेस स्टेशन ( Salyut 1 ) in 1971.
बाद the first 20 years of exploration, फ़ोकस shifted इससे one-off फ़्लाइट to बेदर्दी hardware, ऐसे as the Space शटल program, और from competition to सहयोग as साथ the International स्पेस स्टेशन ( iss ).
साथ the substantial पूर्णता of the ISS following sts-133 in March 2011, योजनाएँ for स्पेस खोजी by the USA remain in फ्लक्स.
Constellation, a बुश Administration कार्यक्रम for a वापसी to the चंद्रमा by 2020 was judged inadequately funded और unrealistic by an expert पुनर्विलोकन panel रिपोर्टिंग in 2009.
the ओबामा प्रशासन प्रस्तावित a revision of Constellation in 2010 to फ़ोकस on the विकास of the काबिलियत for crewed मिशन beyond कम धरती कक्षा ( leo ), envisioning extending the आपरेशन of the iss परे 2020, transferring the विकास of launch वाहनों लिये human क्रू इससे नासा to the निजी sector, और developing प्रौद्योगिकी to enable missions to परे leo, ऐसे as Earth/Moon l1, the Moon, earth/sun l2, near-earth asteroids, और phobos or मंगल orbit.
as of March 2011, the us Senate और हाउस of प्रतिनिधि हैं स्टिल working towards a compromise नासा funding विधेयक, which will probably terminate Constellation and fund development of a भारी लिफ्ट लॉन्च vehicle ( HLLV ).
in the 2000s, the लोगों 's Republic of चीन initiated a कामयाब manned spaceflight program, while the European संघ, जापानी, and India have भी नियोजित भविष्य मानवयुक्त स्पेस missions.
China, Russia, Japan, और इण्डिया have advocated मानवयुक्त missions to the चंद्रमा दौरान the 21st century, while the यूरोपीय Union रै advocated मानवयुक्त missions to दोनो the चंद्रमा और मंगल दौरान the 21st सदी.
इससे the 1990s onwards, private interests began promoting space पर्यटन and then निजी स्पेस exploration of the चंद्रमा ( देखिए google चंद्र x Prize ).
जॉन calvin कूलिज, jr. ( जुलाई 4, 1872january 5, 1933 ) was the 30th अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य ( 1923–1929 ).
a Republican वकील इससे वर्मांट, कूलिज worked उसके रास्ता up the ladder of Massachusetts राज्य politics, आखिरकार becoming governor of कि state.
His conduct during the बोस्टन पुलिस स्ट्राइक of 1919 thrust उसे into the नेशनल spotlight और gave उसे a प्रतिष्ठा as a man of निर्णायक कार्रवाई.
Soon after, he थी निर्वाचित as the 29th वाइस President in 1920 and succeeded to the प्रेसिडेंसी upon the sudden death of वारेन G. Harding in 1923.
निर्वाचित in his अपना सही in 1924, he gained a प्रतिष्ठा as a small-government conservative, और भी as a man जो said very छोटी.
कूलिज restored public confidence in the श्वेत हाउस after the scandals of his predecessor 's प्रशासन, and left दफ्तर साथ considerable लोकप्रियता.
as a Coolidge biographer put it, `` he embodied the spirit और उम्मीदें of the middle class, could interpret उनके longings और एक्स्प्रेस उनके राय.
कि he किया represent the प्रतिभाशाली of the औसत is the most convincing प्रमाण of उसके शक्ति. ''
कुछ बाद criticized कूलिज as भाग of a सामान्य criticism of laissez-faire सरकारी.
His reputation underwent a पुनर्जागरण during the रोनाल्ड Reagan प्रशासन, लकिन the परम मूल्यांकन of उसके प्रेसिडेंसी is still विभाजित between those जो स्वीकृति of his reduction of the आकार of government कार्यक्रम and those जो believe the federal सरकारी चाहिए be अधिक शामिल in regulating and controlling the economy.
एस्प्रेसो is a concentrated पेय brewed by forcing a small amount of nearly खौलते जल under pressure through finely मैदान कॉफी सेम.
एस्प्रेसो प्रायः has a thicker संगति than कॉफी brewed by other methods, a उच्चतर विशेषज्ञता of suspended and dissolved solids, और crema ( अर्थ मलाई, but being a सन्दर्भ to the झाग साथ a creamy बनावट कि forms as a परिणाम of the pressure ).
As a result of the pressurized brewing process the जायका and रसायन in a typical कप of एस्प्रेसो हैं very concentrated.
एस्प्रेसो is the base for अन्य पेय, such as a latte, कापुचीनो, macchiato, मोचा, or americano.
एस्प्रेसो रै more कैफीन प्रति unit volume than सबसे beverages, लकिन the usual सेवारत आकार is smaller—a typical 60 ml ( 2 US द्रव ounce ) of एस्प्रेसो रै 80 to 150 mg of caffeine, little कम than the 95 to 200 mg of a मानक 240 ml ( 8 us द्रव ounces ) cup of drip-brewed कॉफी.
Brian कैथ Kelly ( born अक्तूबर 25, 1961 ) is an अमरीकी फ़ुटबॉल कोच और पूर्व player.

A अनुबंध is an अनुबंध having a lawful object entered into voluntarily by two or अधिक पार्टियों, प्रत्येक of जिसको intends to बनाएँ one or more legal दायित्वों between उन्हें.
the तत्व of a अनुबंध हैं `` offer '' and `` स्वीकृति '' by `` competent व्यक्तियों '' having विधिक क्षमता जो एक्सचेंज `` विचार '' to बनाएँ `` mutuality of दायित्व. ''
Proof of some or सब of ये तत्व may be किया in writing, though अनुबंध may be made entirely orally or by conduct.
the remedy for breach of contract can be `` damages '' in the form of मुआवजे of money or विशिष्ट performance enforced through an आदेश.
Both of ये remedies award the पार्टी at loss the `` लाभ of the सौदेबाजी '' or अपेक्षा damages, which are वृहद than mere रिलायंस damages, as in promissory estoppel.
The parties may be प्राकृतिक व्यक्तियों or juristic व्यक्तियों.
A अनुबंध is a legally enforceable वादा or undertaking that कुछ होगा or will not occur.
the शब्द promise can be प्रयुक्त as a legal synonym for अनुबंध, हालांकि care is जरूरी as a वादा may नहीं have the full खड़ा of a contract, as when it is an अनुबंध without consideration.
अनुबंध law varies greatly from एक jurisdiction to another, सहित मतभेद in आम विधि compared to civil law, the प्रभाव of प्राप्त law, particularly from England in आम विधि countries, and of विधि संहिताबद्ध in regional legislation.
regarding ऑस्ट्रेलियाई अनुबंध विधि लिये उदाहरण, there are 40 प्रासंगिक acts जिससे प्रभाव on the निर्वचन of contract at the Commonwealth ( संघीय / national ) स्तर, and an अतिरिक्त 26 acts at the स्तर of the state of NSW.
In जोड वहीँ हैं 6 अंतरराष्ट्रीय instruments or conventions जिससे are applicable for international dealings, such as the United Nations सम्मेलन on अनुबंध लिये the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Sale of Goods.
sidney पैट्रिक Crosby, ons ( born अगस्त 7, 1987 ) is a कनाडाई पेशेवर ice हॉकी player जो is captain of the पिट्सबर्ग Penguins of the नेशनल Hockey League ( एनएचएल ).
crosby थी drafted पहला overall by the penguins आउट of the Quebec प्रमुख Junior Hockey लीग ( QMJHL ).
दौरान उसके two-year major junior करियर साथ the rimouski océanic, he अर्जित back-to-back CHL Player of the साल awards और led his क्लबों to the 2005 मेमोरियल Cup फाइनल.
nicknamed `` the Next एक ``, he थी एक of the सबसे अत्यधिक regarded ड्राफ्ट चयन in हॉकी history, leading many to refer to the 2005 ड्राफ्ट लॉटरी as the `` Sidney crosby sweepstakes ''.
in उसके पहला NHL ऋतु, crosby समाप्त छठे in लीग स्कोरिंग साथ 102 अंक ( 39 लक्ष्य, 63 assists ) and थी a runner-up for the Calder मेमोरियल ट्रॉफी ( जीती by Alexander ovechkin ).
By उसके दूसरी ऋतु, he led the NHL साथ 120 अंक ( 36 goals, 84 assists ) to capture the आर्ट रॉस ट्रॉफी, becoming the youngest खिलाड़ी और the तभी किशोरावस्था to जीत a स्कोरिंग शीर्षक in any major उत्तर American खेल league.
कि same ऋतु, crosby भी जीती the Hart मेमोरियल Trophy as the पेशेवर Hockey लेखक संघ 's choice लिये सबसे valuable player and the लेस्टर B. पियर्सन पुरस्कार as the NHL खिलाड़ी Association 's चुनाव लिये सबसे बकाया खिलाड़ी, बनने the seventh खिलाड़ी in NHL इतिहास to earn सब three awards in one साल.
Crosby started the 2007–08 season साथ the team 's captaincy and subsequently led them to the 2008 स्टेनली Cup फाइनल, where वे यहूद defeated by the Detroit रेड विंग्स in six games.
The penguins लौटे to the फाइनल against डेट्रॉयट the following year and जीती in seven खेल ; crosby became the youngest कप्तान in एनएचएल history to जीत the स्टेनली कप.
in the 2009–10 ऋतु, crosby scored a career-high 51 लक्ष्य, tying उसे साथ स्टीवन stamkos for the प्रक्षेपास्त्र Richard ट्रॉफी as the league-leader ; साथ 58 assists, he totaled 109 points, दूसरी in the NHL.
दौरान the off-season, Crosby received the Mark मेसियर नेतृत्व पुरस्कार.
in 2010–11, Crosby sustained a concussion as a परिणाम of हिट्स to the सिर in back-to-back games.
The injury बाएँ उसे sidelined for टेन और a half महीने.
however, बाद playing आठ खेल in the 2011–12 ऋतु, crosby 's concussion-like symptoms लौटे in दिसम्बर 2011, और he किया नहीं वापसी until mid-march 2012.
Internationally, Crosby रै represented Canada in numerous tournaments for the country 's junior and मेन 's टीमों.
After स्पर्धा in the 2003 u-18 Junior संसार कप, he represented Canada in back-to-back iihf संसार U20 Championships, winning चांदी in 2004 और सुनहरा in 2005.
at the 2006 iihf संसार Championship, he led the टूर्नामेंट in स्कोरिंग, जबकि also earning शीर्ष आगे और all-star टोली honours.
चार सालो later, crosby थी named to टोली Canada लिये the 2010 Winter Olympics in Vancouver.
playing the संयुक्त राज्य in the सुनहरा पदक game, he scored the game-winning goal in ओवरटाइम.
a संयुक्त राज्य cent, also ज्ञात as a पैनी.
`` my दो सेंट '' ( 2¢ ) और its longer संस्करण `` put my दो cents in '' is an United राज्य ( us ) idiomatic अभिव्यक्ति, लिया इससे the असली अंग्रेज़ी idiom expression : to put in `` my two कौड़ी लायक '' or `` my tuppence लायक. ''
It is प्रयुक्त to preface the अंतरिम stating of one’s opinion.
By विरोधात्मक the राय to follow – suggesting its मान is तभी two सेंट, a बहुत छोटी amount – the उपयोक्ता of the phrase hopes to lessen the प्रभाव of a संभवतः बयान, प्रर्दशित politeness और विनम्रता.
however, it is भी sometimes used with विडंबना जब expressing a strongly felt राय.
The phrase is also used out of आदत to preface uncontentious राय.

the Chinese सिविल War was a सिविल war in चीन fought between forces loyal to the government of the गणतंत्र of चीन led by the kuomintang ( kmt ) और शक्तियां of the कम्युनिस्ट पार्टी of चीन ( CPC ).
the war began in अप्रैल 1927, amidst the उत्तरी expedition, और essentially ended जब major क्रियाशील battles ceased in 1950.
The विरोध आखिरकार resulted in दो de facto states, the Republic of China ( ROC ) in ताईवान और the लोगों 's Republic of चीन ( पीआरसी ) in मेनलैंड चीन, दोनो claiming to be the legitimate government of चीन.
the युद्ध represented an वैचारिक split ( Left vs. Right ) between the Communist CPC, and the kmt 's ब्रांड of Nationalism.
the सिविल war continued intermittently until लेट 1937, जब the two parties formed a Second संयुक्त Front to काउंटर a जापानी invasion.
China 's full-scale सिविल युद्ध resumed in 1946, a year बाद the समाप्त of hostilities साथ जापानी.
After four more years, 1950 देखी the cessation of प्रमुख सैन्य hostilities—with the newly founded People 's Republic of China controlling मेनलैंड चीन ( including Hainan ), और the गणतंत्र of China 's क्षेत्राधिकार being प्रतिबंधित to ताईवान, Penghu, quemoy, matsu और several outlying islands.
The Kuomintang defeat is attributed to several कारकों : Corruption - Chiang लिखा in his diary on जून 1948 that the kmt था failed, नहीं क्युकी of बाह्य दुश्मनों but क्युकी of rot from within.
दमदार initial support from the u.S. diminished, और तब, रोका.
( partly क्युकी of kmt भ्रष्टाचार and anti-democratic regime, और partly क्युकी of the अनिश्चित u.S. विदेशी policy towards Communism between 1945 and 1950 ) ; Communist जमीन reform policy promised poor peasants farmland इससे उनके landlords.
इस ensured PLA लोकप्रिय support.
After the surrender of Japan at the end of संसार War ii, सोवियत शक्तियां turned over their captured जापानी हथियार to the cpc और allowed the CPC to take control of territory in मंचूरिया.
to इस day, no armistice or सलाम treaty has कभी महरूम signed, और it is debated as to the whether the सिविल War has legally ended.
Cross-Strait संबंध have been hindered by सैन्य खतरे और राजनैतिक and आर्थिक pressure, विशेषकर over Taiwan 's राजनैतिक status, साथ both सरकारें officially adhering to a `` one-china नीति. ''
the पीआरसी still actively दावा ताईवान as भाग of इसके territory और continues to threaten the ROC साथ a सैन्य invasion if the आरओसी officially declares independence by बदलना इसके name to और gaining अंतरराष्ट्रीय मान्यता as the गणतंत्र of ताईवान.
the आरओसी mutually दावा mainland चीन, और वे दोनो continue the fight over diplomatic मान्यता.
आज, the युद्ध as such occurs on the राजनैतिक और आर्थिक fronts in the रूप of cross-strait संबंध ; however, the दो पृथक de facto राज्य have close economic ties.

This कॉंग्रेस शामिल the last हाउस of प्रतिनिधि निर्वाचित इससे congressional जिले that were apportioned आधारित on the 2000 जनसांख्यिकी.
In the 2010 मध्यावधि चुनावों, the Republican पार्टी won the बहुमत in the House of प्रतिनिधि.

Wealth in the संयुक्त राज्य is commonly measured in शर्तें of जाल लायक, जिससे is the योग of all assets, सहित घर equity, ऋण सब liabilities.
The total जाल worth of us households and nonprofit संगठन 1945–2009, unadjusted for महंगाई or जनसांख्यिकी change.
For उदाहरण, a household in कब्ज़ा of an $ 800,000 हाउस, $ 5,000 in परस्पर funds, $ 30,000 in गाड़ियाँ, $ 20,000 worth of stock in उनके अपना कम्पनी, and a $ 45,000 ira होता have एसेट totaling $ 900,000.
assuming कि इस household होता have a $ 250,000 mortgage, $ 40,000 in car लोन, and $ 10,000 in credit कार्ड debt, इसके debts would कुल $ 300,000.
subtracting the debts इससे the लायक of इस household 's एसेट ( 900,000 - $ 300,000 = $ 600,000 ), this household होता have a net worth of $ 600,000.
Net worth can vary साथ fluctuations in value of the underlying assets.
the माल —more specifically, the median net worth—of households in the संयुक्त राज्य is varied with संबंध to रेस, education, geographic location और लिंग.
as एक होता expect, households साथ greater income विशेषता the उच्चतम जाल worths, though ऊँची income can नहीं be taken as an always सटीक indicator of जाल worth.
Overall the number of wealthier households is on the वृद्धि, साथ baby boomers hitting the highs of their करियर.
in जोड, माल is unevenly distributed, with the wealthiest 25 % of US households owning 87 % of the wealth in the संयुक्त States, जिससे was $ 54.2 खरब in 2009.
सहित human पूंजी such as कौशल, the संयुक्त Nations estimated the कुल माल of the संयुक्त राज्य in 2008 to be $ 118 trillion.
इस आलेख सौदे साथ Selective पृष्ठीय Rhizotomy ( sdr ) rather than the rhizotomy प्रक्रियाओं लिये pain राहत ; लिये those procedures, which have begun to लो the नाम `` rhizotomy '' in certain instances, see facet rhizotomy and समान.
a rhizotomy ( ) is a पद chiefly referring to a neurosurgical कार्यविधि that selectively destroys problematic nerve जड़ें in the स्पाइनल cord, most often to relieve the लक्षण of neuromuscular conditions ऐसे as spastic diplegia और other forms of spastic दिमागी palsy.
the selective पृष्ठीय rhizotomy ( SDR ) for spastic cerebral palsy रै been the main उपयोग of rhizotomy लिये neurosurgeons specialising in spastic cp चूंकि the 1980s ; in इस सर्जरी, the spasticity-causing nerves are पृथक और तब targeted और नष्ट.
The sensory तंत्रिका जड़ें, where spasticity is located, are first अलग इससे the motor ones, and the तंत्रिका fibres to be काटें हैं तब identified via electromyographic उत्तेजनाओं.
the ones producing spasticity हैं then selectively lesioned with छोटा विद्युत pulses.
in spasticity, rhizotomy precisely लक्ष्य and नष्ट the क्षतिग्रस्त nerves कि don’t receive गामा अमीनो butyric एसिड, which is the core प्रॉब्लम for लोगों with spastic दिमागी palsy.
ये over-firing, non-gaba-absorbing nerves generate असामान्य विद्युत कार्यकलाप दौरान the emg परीक्षण phase in sdr और हैं thus considered to be the सोर्स of the रोगी 's hypertonia ; वे are eliminated साथ the विद्युत pulses एकबार पहचाना, जबकि the बाकी nerves और nerve रूट carrying the correct messages remain fully intact और untouched.
इस अर्थात् कि the spasticity is permanently dissolved, और कि this is done without affecting बेचैन प्रणाली संवेदनशीलता or function in अन्य क्षेत्रों, क्युकी the तभी nerves नष्ट are the over-firing ones जिम्मेदार for the मांसपेशी tightness.
the terms rhizotomy और neurotomy हैं also increasingly becoming interchangeable in the उपचार of chronic वापस पीड़ा इससे degenerative डिस्क बीमारी.
इस is a procedure called a facet rhizotomy और is नहीं a surgical कार्यविधि लकिन is बजाय done on an outpatient basis using a सरल जांच to लागू radiofrequency waves to the impinged pain-causing तंत्रिका root lying between the facet संयुक्त और the vertebral देह.
ऐसे radio frequency तंत्रिका lesioning results in five to आठ or अधिक महीने of पीड़ा राहत पहले the nerve regenerates and another round of the कार्यविधि needs to be performed.
A facet rhizotomy is just एक of अनेक अलग forms of radiofrequency ablation, and इसके उपयोग of the `` rhizotomy '' नाम चाहिए not be उलझन साथ the sdr procedure.

u.S. रूट 75 is a north–south u.S. राजमार्ग.
The राजमार्ग 's उत्तरी terminus is in kittson County, मिनेसोटा, at the Canadian किनारा, where it once जारी as Manitoba राजमार्ग 75 on the अन्य side of the now-closed किनारा crossing.
Its दक्षिणी टर्मिनस is at Interstate 30 और Interstate 45 in डलास, Texas, जहाँ it is ज्ञात as उत्तर Central एक्सप्रेसवे.

Lower Ninth वार्ड is a पड़ोस of the city of New ऑरलियन्स.
as the नाम implies, it is part of the नवीं वार्ड of नई ऑरलियन्स.
the Lower नवीं वार्ड is प्रायः विचार of as the संपूर्ण क्षेत्रफल within नई Orleans downriver of the औद्योगिक Canal ; however, the नगर नियोजन आयोग divides इस area into the Lower Ninth Ward ( 2 ) और पावन Cross ( 3 ) neighborhoods.
the term `` निम्नतर '' refers to इसके स्थान दूर towards the mouth of the मिसिसिपी नदी, `` down '' or `` नीचे '' the बाकी of the नगर in local भौगोलिक शब्दावली.
लकिन the 9th Ward, like all wards in नई ऑरलियन्स, is a मतदान ज़िला.
the 9th Ward was added as a voting district in 1852.
The `` निम्नतर '' 9th वार्ड is रचित of वार्ड 9 जिले 1, 2, 4, और 7 which make up the Holy क्रॉस क्षेत्रफल और वार्ड 9 जिले 3, 5, 6, and 8.
Higher मतदान district numbers in the 9th Ward ( 8-27 ) हैं on the upriver side of the औद्योगिक कनाल.
the क्षेत्रफल came to national ध्यान for इसके devastation in the aftermath of hurricane कैटरीना in 2005.
हबल views of Copernicus crater ( इनसेट ), जिससे is about 58 मील ( 93 km ) चौड़ी
