the Moon is the तभी प्राकृतिक satellite of the Earth, and the fifth largest उपग्रह in the सौर प्रणाली.
it is the largest प्राकृतिक satellite of a ग्रह in the Solar प्रणाली relative to the size of इसके primary, having 27 % the diameter and 60 % the घनत्व of धरती, resulting in its द्रव्यमान.
the Moon is the दूसरी densest उपग्रह बाद io, a उपग्रह of बृहस्पति.
The चंद्रमा is in synchronous रोटेशन साथ Earth, सदा showing the same फेस with इसके निकट side चिह्नित by अंधेरा volcanic मरिया that भरण between the उज्जवल ancient crustal highlands और the prominent प्रभाव craters.
it is the brightest ऑब्जेक्ट in the आसमान after the सूर्य, हालांकि its सतह is दरअसल very dark, with a reflectance similar to कि of कोयले.
Its prominence in the आसमान and इसके नियमित cycle of phases have, चूंकि प्राचीन टाइम्स, बना the चंद्रमा an important सांस्कृतिक influence on भाषा, calendars, आर्ट और mythology.
the चंद्रमा 's gravitational influence produces the ocean tides and the minute lengthening of the दिन.
the चंद्रमा 's वर्तमान कक्षीय distance, परिचय तीस times the diameter of the धरती, कल्याणकारी it to appear लगभग the वही size in the sky as the Sun, allowing it to कवर the सूर्य nearly precisely in कुल solar eclipses.
इस मिलान of apparent visual size is a संयोग.
The चंद्रमा 's रैखिक distance from the धरती is फिलहाल increasing at a rate of 3.82±0.07cm प्रति year, लकिन this रेट is नहीं constant.
the चंद्रमा is विचार to have formed nearly 4.5 अरब सालो पहले, not long बाद the Earth.
हालांकि वहीँ have महरूम several hypotheses लिये its उत्पत्ति in the पास्ट, the वर्तमान सबसे widely accepted explanation is कि the चंद्रमा formed from the debris left over after a दानव प्रभाव between Earth और a मंगल -आकारd देह.
The Moon is the तभी celestial देह अन्य than धरती on which इंसानो have set पैर.
the सोवियत Union 's luna programme थी the पहला to reach the चंद्रमा साथ unmanned spacecraft in 1959 ; the United राज्य ' नासा अपोलो कार्यक्रम हासिल the तभी manned मिशन to date, शुरूआत with the पहला मानवयुक्त चंद्र orbiting mission by अपोलो 8 in 1968, और छह मानवयुक्त lunar अवतरण between 1969 और 1972, with the first होने Apollo 11.
ये missions returned over 380 kg of चंद्र रॉक्स, which have महरूम प्रयुक्त to develop a geological समझना of the चंद्रमा 's origins, the गठन of इसके internal ढांचा, और इसके subsequent इतिहास.
बाद the अपोलो 17 मिशन in 1972, the Moon has been visited तभी by unmanned spacecraft, notably by the फाइनल Soviet Lunokhod रोवर.
चूंकि 2004, जापानी, चीन, इण्डिया, the संयुक्त States, और the यूरोपीय Space एजेंसी have प्रत्येक भेजा चंद्र orbiters.
ये spacecraft have contributed to confirming the डिस्कवरी of चंद्र जल बर्फ in permanently shadowed craters at the poles और bound into the lunar regolith.
भविष्य मानवयुक्त missions to the Moon have महरूम planned, including government as खूब as privately वित्तपोषित प्रयत्न.
the चंद्रमा remains, अंतर्गत the Outer Space Treaty, free to सब राष्ट्र to explore लिये शांतिपूर्ण purposes.
रोनाल्ड विल्सन reagan ( ; February 6, 1911 – जून 5, 2004 ) was the 40th President of the United राज्य ( 1981–1989 ).
prior to that, he थी the 33rd Governor of California ( 1967–1975 ), और a रेडियो, फिल्मी and टेलीविज़न actor.
born in tampico, इलिनोइस, and उठाया in Dixon, reagan was शिक्षित at Eureka कॉलेज, कमाई a Bachelor of कला degree in अर्थशास्त्र और समाजशास्त्र.
After graduating, reagan स्थानांतरित पहला to आयोवा to work as a रेडियो broadcaster and तब, in 1937, to Los Angeles जहाँ he began a career as an actor, पहला in films and बाद television.
कुछ of उसके सबसे notable films शामिल knute rockne, सब अमरीकी ( 1940 ), Kings पंक्ति ( 1942 ), और bedtime लिये Bonzo ( 1951 ).
Reagan परोसा as President of the Screen अभिनेताओं Guild and later as a प्रवक्ता लिये General इलेक्ट्रिक ( ge ) ; his start in राजनीती occurred दौरान उसके work for ge.
Originally a सदस्य of the Democratic पार्टी, his स्थितियाँ began shifting rightward in the 1950s, और he switched to the Republican पार्टी in 1962.
After delivering a rousing speech in support of बैरी Goldwater 's अध्यक्षीय उम्मीदवारी in 1964, he was persuaded to seek the California governorship, जीतना दो सालो बाद and again in 1970.
He थी defeated in उसके चलाएं for the रिपब्लिकन अध्यक्षीय नामांकन in 1968 और in 1976, लकिन won दोनो the नामांकन and general election in 1980, defeating लाज़िम jimmy कार्टर.
as president, reagan implemented sweeping new राजनैतिक और आर्थिक initiatives.
उसके supply-side economic नीतियों, dubbed `` Reaganomics ``, advocated reducing कर rates to spur आर्थिक विकास, controlling the धन supply to reduce inflation, deregulation of the अर्थव्यवस्था, and reducing government spending.
in his first पद he survived an हत्या attempt, took a मुश्किल लकीर against मजदूर संघ, announced a new War on दवाएँ, and ordered an आक्रमण of हरा.
he थी re-elected in a भूस्खलन in 1984, proclaiming कि it was `` morning in America ``.
उसके दूसरी term थी primarily marked by foreign matters, ऐसे as the ending of the Cold युद्ध, the 1986 bombing of Libya, और the revelation of the Iran-Contra affair.
Publicly describing the सोवियत Union as an `` दुष्ट साम्राज्य ``, he समर्थित anti-communist movements विश्वव्यापी और spent उसके पहला term forgoing the strategy of détente by ordering a massive military buildup in an बाहें race साथ the ussr.
Reagan negotiated with Soviet General Secretary मिखाइल गोर्बाचेव, culminating in the inf सन्धि and the घटी of both countries ' नाभिकीय arsenals.
reagan बाएँ दफ्तर in 1989.

A conservative प्रतीक, he ranks अत्यधिक in public opinion polls of U.S. राष्ट्रपतियों और is credited लिये generating an वैचारिक renaissance on the American राजनैतिक सही.
Complete set of scrolls, constituting the entire tanakh.
The tanakh (, or ; भी tenakh, Tenak, Tanach ) is a नाम used in judaism लिये the canon of the Hebrew बाइबल.
the Tanakh is also ज्ञात as the masoretic Text or the Miqra.
The name is an एक्रोनिम formed इससे the आरंभिक यहूदी letters of the masoretic टेक्स्ट 's three परंपरागत subdivisions : The तोरा ( `` Teaching '', also known as the पाँच Books of Moses ), Nevi'im ( `` नबियों '' ) और ketuvim ( `` कृतियाँ '' ) —hence TaNaKh.
the नाम `` Miqra '' ( מקרא ), meaning `` कि जिससे is पढ़ा '', is an वैकल्पिक यहूदी term लिये the tanakh.
The books of the tanakh were relayed साथ an accompanying मौखिक tradition passed on by प्रत्येक पीढी, पुकारा the मौखिक तोरा.

हत्या कोशिशें and भूखंड on राष्ट्रपतियों of the संयुक्त राज्य have महरूम numerous : अधिक than 20 कोशिशें to kill बैठे and पूर्व presidents, as खूब as the Presidents-elect, are ज्ञात.
चार sitting राष्ट्रपतियों have महरूम killed : अब्राहम Lincoln ( the 16th President ), James A. गारफ़ील्ड ( the 20th President ), विलियम mckinley ( the 25th अध्यक्ष ) और जॉन F. कैनेडी ( the 35th अध्यक्ष ).

हालांकि the इतिहासकार J.W. क्लार्क रै सुझाया कि most American assassinations were नीतियां motivated actions, carried out by तर्कसंगत मेन, नहीं सब ऐसे attacks have been undertaken for राजनैतिक reasons.
Some हमलावर था questionable दिमागी स्थिरता, and a few were judged legally insane.
Since the वाइस President of the United राज्य रै for more than a सदी महरूम निर्वाचित इससे the same political party as the President, the assassination of the President is unlikely to result in major नीति परिवर्तन.
इस may बताइये why राजनैतिक समूह typically do नहीं make ऐसे हमले.

ओक्लाहोमा ( ) ( pawnee : uukuhuúwa, cay : gahnawiyoˀgeh ) is a राज्य located in वेस्ट South सेंट्रल संयुक्त राज्य.
Oklahoma is the 20th most extensive and the 28th most populous of the 50 United राज्य.
The राज्य 's नाम is निकला इससे the choctaw words okla and humma, अर्थ `` red लोगों '', और it is known informally by इसके nickname, The Sooner State.
formed by the संयोजन of Oklahoma territory और Indian territory on November 16, 1907, Oklahoma थी the 46th राज्य to enter the संघ.
Its residents हैं known as Oklahomans or, informally `` okies '', and इसके पूंजी and largest city is ओक्लाहोमा नगर.
a प्रमुख producer of natural gas, oil, and कृषि, ओक्लाहोमा relies on an आर्थिक base of aviation, energy, दूरसंचार, और biotechnology.
it has एक of the fastest growing economies in the स्वदेश, रैंकिंग among the शीर्ष राज्य in प्रति capita income growth and सकल घरेलू product growth.
Oklahoma नगर and तुलसा serve as Oklahoma 's प्राथमिक आर्थिक anchors, साथ nearly two thirds of oklahomans living भीतर उनके metropolitan statistical क्षेत्रों.
With छोटी mountain ranges, प्रेयरी, mesas, और पूर्वी वनों, सबसे of ओक्लाहोमा झूठ in the ग्रेट मैदान और the u.s. आंतरिक हाइलैंड्स —a प्रदेश especially prone to कठोर मौसम.
in addition to having a व्यापकता of अंग्रेज़ी, German, स्कॉटिश, Irish and Native अमरीकी ancestry, अधिक than 25 देशी अमरीकी languages हैं बोला in Oklahoma, second तभी to कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
Oklahoma is located on a confluence of three major अमरीकी सांस्कृतिक regions and historically परोसा as a रूट for cattle drives, a destination लिये southern settlers, और a government-sanctioned territory for देशी Americans.
Redwall, by ब्रायन ज़ाक, is a श्रेणी of children 's काल्पनिक novels.
it is the शीर्षक of the पहला book of the series, प्रकाशित in 1986, as well as the name of the ऐबी प्रदर्शित in the book और the name of an एनिमेटेड tv series based on three of the novels ( Redwall, Mattimeo, और Martin the Warrior ), which पहला aired in 1999.
the किताबे हैं primarily aimed at पुरानी children, लकिन have प्रशंसक of सब ages.
वहीँ have महरूम twenty-two novels and two चित्र किताबे published.
The twenty-second, और फाइनल, अनोखा, the दुष्ट क्रू, was मरणोपरांत released on May 3, 2011.
Natural गैस is प्रायः measured by volume in the संयुक्त States and is stated in घन फीट.
A घन पैर of गैस is the amount of गैस needed to भरण a आवाज़ of one cubic पैर under नियत शर्तें of pressure and temperature.to measure larger amounts of प्राकृतिक गैस, a `` therm '' is used to denote 100 cubic feet, और `` mcf '' is प्रयुक्त to denote 1,000 घन फीट.
to provide वृहद सटीकता in comparing fuels, उर्जा सामग्री is measured in शर्तें of `` अंग्रेजों Thermal Units ( btu 's ). ''
a BTU is the राशि of heat जरूरी to उठाएँ one पाउंड of जल ( approximately a pint ), one degree फ़ारेनहाइट at or close to its पाइंट of maximum घनत्व.
One British therm ( symbol thm ) is a non- si unit of heat उर्जा बराबर to 100,000 अंग्रेजों thermal units ( btu ).
it is लगभग the energy equivalent of burning 100 cubic फीट ( प्रायः referred to as 1 CCF ) of प्राकृतिक gas.
Since ( Natural गैस ) मीटर measure आवाज़ and नहीं उर्जा सामग्री, a therm factor is used by ( Natural ) गैस companies to convert the आवाज़ of गैस used to इसके ऊष्मा समतुल्य, और यूँ गणना the वास्तविक energy use.
The therm फ़ैक्टर is प्रायः in the units therms/ccf.
It will vary साथ the mix of hydrocarbons in the natural gas.
प्राकृतिक gas with a उच्चतर than average विशेषज्ञता of इथेन, प्रोपेन or butane होगा have a उच्चतर therm फ़ैक्टर.
impurities, such as कार्बन dioxide or nitrogen, निम्नतर the therm factor.
The आवाज़ of the गैस is calculated as if measured at मानक तापमान और दबाव ( STP ).
the ऊष्मा सामग्री of natural गैस is solely dependent on the संयोजन of the गैस, और is स्वतंत्र of तापमान and pressure.
एक therm is बराबर to about 105.5 megajoules, 25,200 kilocalories or 29.3 kilowatt-hours.
एक therm can भी be provided by about of प्राकृतिक गैस.
the therm sometimes has been उलझन with the thermie ( देखिए नीचे ).
the names of दोनो इकाई come इससे the Greek word लिये heat.
A thermie ( th ) is a मीट्रिक unit of ऊष्मा उर्जा, part of the meter-tonne-second प्रणाली sometimes प्रयुक्त by European engineers.
The thermie is equal to the amount of उर्जा जरूरी to raise the तापमान of 1 tonne of जल by 1 °c.
The thermie is समतुल्य to 1,000 kilocalories, 4.1868 megajoules or 3968.3 btu.
the American सिविल War ( ACW ), also ज्ञात as the War between the राज्य or simply the Civil War ( see naming ), थी a civil war fought from 1861 to 1865 between the संयुक्त राज्य ( the `` संघ '' or the `` उत्तर '' ) और several Southern स्लेव states कि घोषित their secession और formed the confederate राज्य of अमेरिका ( the `` confederacy '' or the `` दक्षिण '' ).
The war था its उत्पत्ति in the समस्या of गुलामी, विशेषकर the extension of गुलामी into the पश्चिमी territories.
विदेशी शक्तियां किया नहीं intervene.
After चार years of bloody कॉम्बैट that left over 600,000 soldiers मुर्दे and नष्ट much of the South 's infrastructure, the confederacy collapsed, slavery थी abolished, and the मुश्किल पुनर्निर्माण प्रक्रम of restoring नेशनल एकता और guaranteeing rights to the freed स्लेव began.
In the 1860 अध्यक्षीय चुनाव, republicans, led by अब्राहम lincoln, opposed expanding गुलामी into संयुक्त States ' territories.
Lincoln won, लकिन पहले his उद्घाटन on March 4, 1861, seven cotton-based स्लेव राज्य formed the confederacy.
outgoing Democratic President James Buchanan और the आवक Republicans अस्वीकृत secession as illegal.
lincoln 's inaugural address declared उसके administration would नहीं initiate सिविल युद्ध.
Eight remaining स्लेव states continued to reject calls लिये secession.
confederate शक्तियां जब्त numerous संघीय दुर्गों within territory claimed by the confederacy.
a Peace सम्मेलन failed to find a सुलह, और both sides prepared लिये युद्ध.
the confederates assumed कि यूरोपीय देशों यहूद so निर्भर on `` किंग कपास `` that they would intervene ; none did और none पहचाना the नई confederate राज्य of America.
Hostilities began on अप्रैल 12, 1861, when confederate शक्तियां fired upon फोर्ट sumter, a कुंजी fort held by संघ सैनिकों in दक्षिण Carolina.
lincoln पुकारा for each राज्य to provide troops to retake the फोर्ट ; नतीजतन, four more स्लेव राज्य joined the Confederacy, bringing उनके कुल to ग्यारह.
The संघ जल्द नियंत्रित the border states and established a naval blockade that अबोध the दक्षिणी अर्थव्यवस्था.
the पूर्वी थिएटर थी inconclusive in 1861–62.
the पतझड़ 1862 confederate campaign into मेरीलैंड ( a संघ state ) ended with confederate रिट्रीट at the Battle of Antietam, dissuading अंग्रेजों intervention.
Lincoln जारी the Emancipation Proclamation, जिससे बना समाप्ति slavery a युद्ध goal.
to the west, by गर्मियाँ 1862 the संघ नष्ट the confederate नदी navy, तब much of their western armies, and the संघ at vicksburg split the confederacy in two at the मिसिसिपी River.
in 1863, रॉबर्ट E. Lee 's Confederate incursion north ended at the बैटल of gettysburg.
पश्चिमी सफलताओं led to Ulysses S. Grant कमांड of सब संघ armies in 1864.
In the Western थिएटर, William T. Sherman drove ईस्ट to capture अटलांटा and marched to the समुद्र, destroying Confederate अवसंरचना साथ the रास्ता.
the Union marshaled the resources and manpower to attack the confederacy इससे all दिशानिर्देश, और could afford to लड़ो battles of अपघर्षण through the Overland अभियान towards रिचमंड, the confederate पूंजी.
the defending confederate फौज विफल, leading to Lee 's surrender to ग्रान्ट at Appomattox Court हाउस on अप्रैल 9, 1865.
The अमरीकी सिविल War थी one of the earliest सच्चा industrial wars.
Railroads, the telegraph, steamships, and mass-produced weapons were employed extensively.
the mobilization of civilian कारखानों, खानों, shipyards, बैंको, transportation and खाना आपूर्तियाँ सब foreshadowed संसार युद्ध i.
it remains the deadliest युद्ध in American history, resulting in the मौतों of an estimated 750,000 सैनिको and an undetermined क्रमांक of civilian हताहत.
इतिहासकार John Huddleston estimates the मौत toll at टेन प्रतिशत of all Northern males 20–45 सालो old, and 30 प्रतिशत of all Southern श्वेत males aged 18–40.
विलियम Bruce जेनर ( born अक्तूबर 28, 1949 ) is a पूर्व u.S. track and फ़ील्ड खिलाड़ी, प्रेरक स्पीकर, socialite, टेलीविज़न व्यक्तित्व और बिजनेसमैन.
He won the सुनहरा पदक लिये decathlon in the मॉन्ट्रियल 1976 Summer ओलंपिक.
Following his Olympic जीत and the related recognition, he शादीशुदा क्रिस कार्दशियन, and उसके professional करियर evolved into होने a television हस्ती.
By 1981, he था starred in अनेक made-for-tv फिल्मों and थी Erik एस्ट्राडा 's बदलना on the शीर्ष रेटेड tv श्रेणी CHiPs.
He रै six children : Burt, केसी, ब्रैंडन, ब्रोडी, Kendall and काइली.

escherichia कोलाई ( ; commonly abbreviated E. coli ) is a gram-negative, rod-shaped bacterium that is commonly found in the निम्नतर intestine of warm-blooded organisms ( endotherms ).
सबसे E. coli strains हैं हानिरहित, लकिन some serotypes can कारण serious food विषाक्तता in इंसानो, और हैं occasionally जिम्मेदार लिये उत्पाद recalls due to food संदूषण.
the हानिरहित strains हैं भाग of the normal फ्लोरा of the gut, and can benefit their होस्ट by producing विटामिन K2, and by preventing the establishment of रोगजनक bacteria भीतर the intestine.
E. coli and related bacteria constitute परिचय 0.1 % of आंत फ्लोरा, और fecal–oral transmission is the प्रमुख रूट through जिससे pathogenic strains of the bacterium cause बीमारी.
Cells are समर्थ to जीवित outside the body for a सीमित राशि of समय, जिससे makes उन्हें आदर्श indicator जीवों to परीक्षण पर्यावरणीय samples लिये fecal संदूषण.
वहीँ is, however, a growing body of research कि has examined environmentally persistent E. कोलाई जिससे can जीवित लिये extended periods outside of the host.
the bacterium can भी be grown easily and inexpensively in a प्रयोगशाला सेटिंग, और रै been intensively investigated लिये over 60 years.
E. coli is the most widely studied prokaryotic मॉडल organism, and an important प्रजाति in the fields of जैवप्रौद्योगिकी and microbiology, जहाँ it रै परोसा as the host सजीव लिये the बहुमत of work with recombinant डीएनए.
क्षेत्रफल code 217 is the उत्तर American टेलीफोन क्षेत्रफल कोड for much of पश्चिमी and central इलिनोइस.
The 217 area includes Illinois ' पूंजी, springfield, plus Champaign, Urbana, decatur, Danville, क्विंसी, और rantoul.

ओज़ोन depletion describes two पृथक लकिन सम्बन्धित phenomena observed since the लेट 1970s : a स्थिर decline of about 4 % प्रति दशक in the कुल आवाज़ of ओज़ोन in धरती 's stratosphere ( the ओज़ोन परत ), और a much larger springtime घटी in stratospheric ozone over धरती 's polar regions.
the latter घटना is referred to as the ओज़ोन hole.
in जोड to ये well-known stratospheric phenomena, there are also springtime polar tropospheric ozone depletion events.
The विवरण of ध्रुवीय ozone hole formation differ from कि of mid-latitude thinning, but the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण process in दोनो is catalytic विनाश of ओज़ोन by atomic हैलोजन्स.
The प्रमुख सोर्स of ये हैलोजन atoms in the stratosphere is photodissociation of man-made halocarbon refrigerants ( CFCs, freons, halons ).
These यौगिकों are transported into the stratosphere बाद being emitted at the सतह.
Both प्रकार of ओज़ोन depletion यहूद observed to बढ़ाएँ as emissions of halo-carbons increased.
cfcs and अन्य contributory substances हैं referred to as ozone-depleting substances ( ods ).
चूंकि the ozone layer रोकता सबसे नुकसानदेह UVB wavelengths ( 280–315 nm ) of ultraviolet लाइट ( uv लाइट ) from गुजर through the Earth 's atmosphere, observed और प्रक्षिप्त decreases in ओज़ोन have generated विश्वव्यापी चिंता leading to अपनाना of the Montreal प्रोटोकॉल that bans the production of CFCs, halons, and अन्य ozone-depleting रसायन ऐसे as carbon tetrachloride और trichloroethane.
it is suspected कि a variety of biological consequences ऐसे as increases in स्किन cancer, cataracts, damage to पौधे, and कटौती of प्लवक populations in the ocean 's photic मण्डल may result इससे the increased uv एक्सपोज़र due to ओज़ोन depletion.
The प्रस्तावना to the United States संविधान is a brief introductory बयान of the Constitution 's आधारभूत purposes और guiding principles.
it states in general शर्तें, and न्यायालयों have referred to it as reliable प्रमाण of, the founding fathers ' intentions regarding the संविधान 's meaning and कया वे hoped the Constitution होता achieve as it pertains to सब of the people of the United States.
as the phrase, `` we the लोगों '' suggests कि the नई सरकारी originates इससे the लोगों of the United राज्य और it सेट into motion a सवाल as it pertains to कि विशाल population concerning the individual rights और equality among all people ; इस can be seen सबसे broadly in the divide between republicanism और सोशल democracy.

The शॉट put ( सुनाया ) is a track और field इवेंट involving `` throwing '' / '' putting '' ( फेंकना in a pushing motion ) a heavy spherical ऑब्जेक्ट —the shot—as far as possible.
The शॉट put प्रतियोगिता लिये मेन रै महरूम a भाग of the आधुनिक ओलंपिक चूंकि उनके पुनरुद्धार in 1896, महिलाओं 's प्रतियोगिता began in 1948.
Map of the United राष्ट्र ( UN ) सदस्य राज्य, साथ उनके territories ( सहित निर्भर territories ) recognized by the un in ब्लू
There are संयुक्त राष्ट्र ( UN ) सदस्य राज्य, and प्रत्येक of उन्हें is a सदस्य of the United Nations सामान्य सभा.
the मापदण्ड लिये admission of नई members हैं नियत आउट in the संयुक्त राष्ट्र Charter, अध्याय II, आलेख 4:
A recommendation लिये प्रवेश इससे the सुरक्षा Council requires affirmative मत from at least नौ of the council 's fifteen members, with none of the five स्थाई members मतदान विरूद्ध.
The सुरक्षा परिषद 's अनुशंसा must तब be subsequently स्वीकृत in the सामान्य सभा by a two-thirds बहुमत vote.
in principle, तभी sovereign राज्य can become UN members, और currently सब un सदस्यों are sovereign राज्य ( हालांकि a few members यहूद not sovereign when they joined the un ).
Because a राज्य can तभी be admitted to the UN by the approval of the Security Council और the सामान्य सभा, a number of states कि may be माना sovereign states according to the montevideo सम्मेलन criteria are नहीं सदस्यों because the un does not consider them to possess sovereignty, मुख्यतः due to the कमी of अंतरराष्ट्रीय मान्यता or opposition from certain सदस्यों.
In जोड to the member राज्य, the un भी आमंत्रण non-member states ( फिलहाल two : the Holy देखिए and फिलिस्तीन ), intergovernmental संगठन, and अन्य अंतरराष्ट्रीय organizations और entities जिनकी statehood or sovereignty are नहीं precisely पारिभाषित, to become observers at the General Assembly, allowing उन्हें to participate और speak, लकिन not vote, in सामान्य Assembly बैठक.
the Eiffel मीनार (, ) is an आयरन lattice मीनार स्तिथ on the champ de Mars in पेरिस, नामित after the इंजीनियर gustave Eiffel, जिनकी company designed and built the tower.
erected in 1889 as the प्रवेश arch to the 1889 संसार 's मेला, it रै become दोनो a global सांस्कृतिक icon of फ़्रांस और one of the सबसे recognizable structures in the world.
the मीनार is the tallest ढांचा in Paris and the most-visited paid स्मारक in the world ; 7.1 लाख लोगों ascended it in 2011.
The third level observatory 's अपर platform is at the उच्चतम accessible to public in the European संघ और the highest in यूरोपीय as long as the मंच of the Ostankino Tower, at, remains बंद as a परिणाम of the fire of अगस्त 2000.
the मीनार received its 250 millionth आगंतुक in 2010.
The tower स्टैंड tall, परिचय the वही ऊँचाई as an 81-storey भवन.
During its निर्माण, the एफिल मीनार surpassed the वॉशिंगटन स्मारक to assume the शीर्षक of the tallest man-made structure in the संसार, a शीर्षक it held लिये 41 years, until the Chrysler Building in नई यॉर्क City थी built in 1930.
Because of the जोड, in 1957, of the antenna atop the Eiffel मीनार, it is now taller than the क्रिसलर भवन.
नहीं सहित ब्रॉडकास्ट एन्टेना, it is the second-tallest ढांचा in France, after the Millau Viaduct.
The tower रै three स्तर लिये visitors.

the कनाडाई फ़ुटबॉल लीग or cfl ( ' [ lcf ] in French ) is a professional sports लीग located in Canada.
the cfl is the उच्चतम स्तर of competition in कनाडाई फ़ुटबॉल, a form of gridiron football closely सम्बन्धित to अमरीकी फ़ुटबॉल.
Its आठ वर्तमान टीमों, which हैं located in eight separate शहरों, are विभाजित into two विभाजन of four teams प्रत्येक — the ईस्ट प्रभाग और the वेस्ट प्रभाग.
The league 's 19-week नियमित ऋतु रनों इससे late जून to जल्दी नवम्बर ; प्रत्येक team plays 18 खेल with one bye week.
Following the regular season, the three टीमों साथ the बेहतरीन रिकॉर्ड in their प्रभाग ( except if the चौथी प्लेस टोली in one division रै a better रिकार्ड than the तीसरा प्लेस team in the other division, when the team साथ the बेहतर record makes the playoffs and `` crosses over '' to the other division 's playoff ) compete in the लीग 's three-week डिवीजनल playoffs, which culminate in the late-November धूसर कप championship, the देश 's largest सालाना खेल और टेलीविज़न इवेंट.
the CFL was officially संस्थापित on जनवरी 19, 1958, बनाना it the second oldest gridiron football league in उत्तर अमेरिका still in आपरेशन, although all इसके teams long predate the आधुनिक गठन of the लीग.
it is the highest level of खेल in Canadian फ़ुटबॉल, the सबसे popular football लीग in कनाडा, और the second-most लोकप्रिय major खेल लीग in Canada, after the National Hockey लीग.
हालांकि ice हॉकी is Canada 's सबसे लोकप्रिय खेल, the cfl रै increased the popularity of कनाडाई football in क्यूबेक and पश्चिमी कनाडा.
कनाडाई football is भी played at amateur levels ( i.e. youth, high school, cjfl, QJFL, cis और वरिष्ठ लीग ऐसे as the Alberta Football लीग ).
the 2010s होगा be a significant decade for the cfl in शर्तें of विकास, as teams have संवर, विस्तारित स्टेडियम, or plan to निर्माण entirely नई stadiums.
The Montreal अलॉतेस संपन्नता इस first, adding 5,000 seats to Percival molson मेमोरियल स्टेडियम in समय लिये the 2010 cfl ऋतु.
the एडमॉन्टन एस्किमोस और कैला Stampeders भी renovated their respective स्टेडियम और सुविधाएं लिये the 2010 season.
in 2011, the BC Lions निभाई under a नई, retractable roof in BC Place after spending एक और a हाफ सीज़न at साम्राज्य Field.
तब the Winnipeg ब्लू बमवर्षक होगा खेल in an entirely नई स्टेडियम at the University of मनिटोबा, अनुसूचित to open in time for the 2013 ऋतु.
The हैमिल्टन tiger-cats, Saskatchewan roughriders and the नई Ottawa franchise हैं भी looking at नई or extensively-renovated स्टेडियम in the following years.
वहीँ हैं also उम्मीदें of expanding the league to अटलांटिक कनाडा ( ideally basing a टोली in either the अधिक populated halifax, or the more centralized Moncton ), as 2010 and 2011 था नियमित season games hosted in moncton.
according to sports historian Douglas brei, the कनाडाई Football लीग holds the distinction of होने the only पेशेवर खेल लीग in उत्तर America, major or नाबालिग league, in which प्रत्येक existing franchise has won at तनिक one league शीर्षक जबकि in their current location.
Each एंटीबॉडी बांधता to a विशिष्ट antigen ; an बातचीत similar to a ताला और कुंजी.
An एंटीबॉडी ( ab ), भी ज्ञात as an immunoglobulin ( Ig ), is a large Y-shaped प्रोटीन उत्पादित by b-cells कि is used by the प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली to identify और neutralize foreign वस्तुएँ such as जीवाणु और वाइरस.
The एंटीबॉडी recognizes a अद्वितीय part of the foreign target, पुकारा an antigen.
Each टिप of the `` y '' of an antibody contains a paratope ( a structure analogous to a ताला ) कि is विशिष्ट लिये एक particular epitope ( similarly analogous to a कुंजी ) on an प्रतिजन, allowing these दो structures to bind साथ साथ precision.
using इस बाइंडिंग यांत्रिकी, an एंटीबॉडी can टैग a microbe or an संक्रमित cell लिये आक्रमण by other भाग of the प्रतिरक्षा system, or can neutralize इसके निशाना सीधे ( for उदाहरण, by ब्लॉकिंग a भाग of a microbe कि is अनिवार्य for इसके आक्रमण और अस्तित्व ).
the production of antibodies is the प्रमुख function of the humoral प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली.
antibodies हैं स्रावित by a type of श्वेत blood cell called a plasma cell.
Antibodies can occur in दो physical फ़ॉर्म, a soluble रूप कि is secreted इससे the cell, and a झिल्ली -bound form that is attached to the सतह of a B कोशिका and is referred to as the B कोशिका receptor ( bcr ).
the bcr is तभी मिला on the surface of b कोशिकाएं और facilitates the सक्रियण of these कोशिकाएं और उनके subsequent differentiation into either एंटीबॉडी factories पुकारा plasma कोशिकाएं, or मेमोरी b कोशिकाएं that will survive in the देह और remember that same प्रतिजन so the b cells can respond तेज़ upon future एक्सपोज़र.
In most मामले, बातचीत of the b कोशिका साथ a T हेल्पर कोशिका is necessary to उपज पूरा activation of the b कोशिका और, इसलिए, एंटीबॉडी generation following प्रतिजन binding.
Soluble antibodies हैं released into the रक्त और ऊतक fluids, as खूब as many secretions to continue to सर्वेक्षण for invading microorganisms.
Antibodies are glycoproteins belonging to the immunoglobulin superfamily ; the शर्तें एंटीबॉडी and immunoglobulin are often used interchangeably.
Antibodies हैं typically बना of मौलिक structural units—each with दो विशाल heavy जंजीरों और दो छोटी light chains.
There are several अलग types of antibody भारी जंजीरों, और several अलग kinds of antibodies, जिससे हैं grouped into अलग isotypes आधारित on जिससे heavy chain वे possess.
पाँच अलग एंटीबॉडी isotypes हैं known in mammals, जिससे perform different भूमिकाएँ, और सहायता सीधा the उचित प्रतिरक्षा response लिये each अलग type of विदेशी ऑब्जेक्ट वे encounter.
हालांकि the general structure of सब antibodies is बहुत समान, a छोटी region at the टिप of the protein is extremely परिवर्तनीय, allowing millions of antibodies साथ slightly अलग टिप structures, or antigen बाइंडिंग sites, to exist.
इस प्रदेश is known as the hypervariable region.
प्रत्येक of ये विसंगतियाँ can bind to a अलग प्रतिजन.
This विशाल विविधता of antibodies allows the प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली to recognize an बराबर चौड़ी किस्में of antigens.
the विशाल और विविध जनसांख्यिकी of antibodies is generated by random combinations of a नियत of जीन segments कि encode अलग प्रतिजन बाइंडिंग साइट ( or paratopes ), followed by यादृच्छिक mutations in इस area of the antibody जीन, which बनाएँ further विविधता.
एंटीबॉडी genes also re-organize in a प्रक्रम पुकारा क्लास switching कि परिवर्तन the आधार of the भारी chain to another, बनाना a different isotype of the एंटीबॉडी कि retains the antigen विशिष्ट परिवर्तनीय प्रदेश.
This allows a सिंगल antibody to be प्रयुक्त by several अलग भाग of the प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली.
the प्रतीक प्रयुक्त by the zodiac कातिल to sign उसके पत्राचार
the zodiac Killer थी a सीरियल कातिल जो operated in Northern कैलिफ़ोर्निया in the लेट 1960s और जल्दी 1970s.
the killer 's identity remains unknown.
The zodiac murdered पीड़ितों in benicia, Vallejo, झील Berryessa, और सैन Francisco between December 1968 और अक्तूबर 1969.
चार मेन और three women between the आयु of 16 and 29 were targeted.
The कातिल originated the नाम `` Zodiac '' in a श्रेणी of taunting अक्षर sent to the लोकल Bay Area दबायें.
ये अक्षर शामिल चार cryptograms ( or ciphers ).
of the चार cryptograms भेजा, तभी एक रै been definitively हल.
संदिग्धों have महरूम named by विधि प्रवर्तन and amateur जांचकर्ताओं, but no conclusive evidence रै surfaced.
in अप्रैल 2004, the सैन Francisco पुलिस विभाग चिह्नित the case `` निष्क्रिय '', yet re-opened the मामला at कुछ point prior to March 2007.
the मामला also remains open in the नगर of vallejo, as खूब as in नापा काउंटी और solano काउंटी.
the कैलिफ़ोर्निया Department of Justice रै कायम an open मामला file on the zodiac murders चूंकि 1969.
Jennings is a small नगर in और the parish seat of जेफरसन Davis Parish, Louisiana, संयुक्त राज्य, निकट झील चार्ल्स.

it is भी भाग of the larger झील charles-jennings संयुक्त सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रफल.
nanotechnology ( sometimes shortened to `` nanotech '' ) is the हेरफेर of पदार्थ on an atomic और आणविक स्केल.
The earliest, फैली description of nanotechnology referred to the particular technological goal of precisely manipulating atoms और molecules for fabrication of macroscale उत्पाद, also अभी referred to as आणविक nanotechnology.
a अधिक generalized वर्णन of nanotechnology थी subsequently स्थापित by the नेशनल nanotechnology पहल, which defines nanotechnology as the manipulation of matter with at least one आयाम sized from 1 to 100 nanometers.
This definition reflects the फैक्ट कि क्वांटम mechanical प्रभाव हैं important at इस quantum-realm स्केल, और so the परिभाषा shifted इससे a particular technological goal to a शोध श्रेणी समावेशी of all प्रकार of शोध और technologies that deal साथ the special गुण of matter कि occur below the given आकार दहलीज.
It is therefore आम to see the बहुवचन रूप `` nanotechnologies '' as खूब as `` nanoscale technologies '' to refer to the व्यापक दायरा of research और applications जिनकी आम trait is आकार.
Because of the किस्में of संभावित अनुप्रयोग ( सहित industrial and military ), सरकारें have invested billions of डॉलर in nanotechnology research.
through its नेशनल Nanotechnology Initiative, the USA has invested 3.7 billion डॉलर.
the यूरोपीय संघ has invested 1.2 अरब and Japan 750 million डॉलर.
Nanotechnology as पारिभाषित by size is naturally बहुत broad, सहित फ़ील्ड of विज्ञान as विविध as सतह विज्ञान, organic chemistry, molecular जीवविज्ञान, semiconductor physics, microfabrication, etc.
the संबद्ध शोध and applications हैं equally विविध, ranging from एक्सटेंशन of conventional यंत्र भौतिकी to completely new approaches आधारित upon molecular self-assembly, इससे developing नई materials with आयाम on the nanoscale to direct control of matter on the परमाणु scale.
Scientists फिलहाल बहस the भविष्य implications of nanotechnology.
Nanotechnology may be समर्थ to create अनेक new सामग्री and devices with a विशाल range of applications, ऐसे as in आयुर्विज्ञान, इलेक्ट्रॉनिक्स, biomaterials और उर्जा production.
on the अन्य hand, nanotechnology उठाता अनेक of the वही मुद्दे as कोई नई प्रौद्योगिकी, including चिंताएं परिचय the toxicity और environmental प्रभाव of nanomaterials, और उनके संभावित प्रभाव on वैश्विक अर्थशास्त्र, as खूब as अटकलें परिचय विभिन्न doomsday scenarios.
These चिंताएं have led to a debate among advocacy समूह और governments on whether special regulation of nanotechnology is warranted.
मैप of the पूर्वी bloc
the पद Eastern bloc or Communist bloc refers to the पूर्व कम्युनिस्ट राज्य of सेंट्रल और Eastern यूरोपीय, generally the सोवियत संघ और the देशों of the वॉरसॉ अनुबंध.
The शर्तें कम्युनिस्ट Bloc and Soviet bloc were भी प्रयुक्त to denote groupings of राज्य aligned with the सोवियत Union, हालांकि ये शर्तें might शामिल राज्य बाहर सेंट्रल और पूर्वी यूरोपीय.
The New जर्सी gubernatorial चुनाव of 2009 took place on November 3, 2009.
लोकतांत्रिक राज्यपाल jon corzine थी कार्यशील लिये a second पद and थी being challenged by रिपब्लिकन क्रिस क्रिस्टी, स्वतंत्र Christopher daggett and nine अन्य, in addition to several write-in उम्मीदवार.
Christie जीती the election, साथ परिचय 48.5 प्रतिशत of the vote, to 44.9 percent for corzine और 5.8 प्रतिशत for Daggett.
क्रिस्टी won the largest हाशिया for a first term Republican चूंकि 1969.
Christie assumed office on जनवरी 19, 2010.
This was the first चुनाव to भरण the newly निर्मित दफ्तर of लेफ्टिनेंट Governor.
the candidates लिये राज्यपाल और लेफ्टिनेंट राज्यपाल यहूद joined साथ as a single चुनाव, so that मतदाता किया नहीं have the opportunity to विभाजित the टिकट.
किम guadagno, Christie 's running mate, became New Jersey 's first लेफ्टिनेंट राज्यपाल following उसके inauguration.
Health परवाह in the United States is provided by अनेक distinct संगठन.
Health care सुविधाएं are largely स्वामित्व और संचालित by निजी सेक्टर व्यवसायों.
स्वास्थ्य बीमे लिये पब्लिक सेक्टर employees is primarily provided by the सरकारी.
60-65 % of healthcare प्रावधान and spending comes from कार्यक्रम such as medicare, Medicaid, tricare, the Children 's स्वास्थ्य Insurance कार्यक्रम, और the दिग्गजों स्वास्थ्य Administration.
Most of the population अंतर्गत 65 is insured by their or a परिवार सदस्य 's employer, some ख़रीदे स्वास्थ्य बीमे on उनके own, and the remainder हैं uninsured.
Of 17 high-income देशों studied by the नेशनल संस्थान of स्वास्थ्य in 2013, the United राज्य was at or near the नीचे in infant मृत्यु, दिल और फेफड़ों disease, sexually transmitted infections, adolescent pregnancies, injuries, homicides, और दरों of disability.
साथ, such issues place the U.S. at the नीचे of the list लिये जीवन प्रत्याशा.
on औसत, a u.S. male can be expected to live लगभग चार fewer सालो than those in the top-ranked country.
according to the World स्वास्थ्य Organization ( जो ), the United States spent more on स्वास्थ्य परवाह per capita ( $ 7,146 ), and अधिक on स्वास्थ्य care as percentage of its जीडीपी ( 15.2 % ), than any other स्वदेश in 2008.
The राष्ट्रमंडल निधि क्रमित the United राज्य last in the विशेषता of स्वास्थ्य परवाह among similar countries, and notes u.S. परवाह लागत the सबसे.
the u.S. Census Bureau reported कि 49.9 लाख निवासियों, 16.3 % of the जनसांख्यिकी, were uninsured in 2010 ( up इससे 49.0 लाख निवासियों, 16.1 % of the जनसांख्यिकी, in 2009 ).
a 2004 Institute of आयुर्विज्ञान ( iom ) रपट कहा : `` The संयुक्त States is among the few industrialized nations in the world that करता नहीं guarantee अभिगम to स्वास्थ्य care लिये its जनसांख्यिकी. ''
A 2004 oecd रपट said : `` साथ the एक्सेप्शन of मैक्सिको, Turkey, and the संयुक्त States, all oecd countries had हासिल universal or near-universal ( at तनिक 98.4 % insured ) कवरेज of उनके populations by 1990. ''
a 2010 रपट observed that कमी of स्वास्थ्य बीमे causes roughly 48,000 unnecessary मौतों प्रत्येक year in the संयुक्त States.
in 2007, 62.1 % of filers for bankruptcies claimed high medical expenses.

in physiology, देह जल is the water सामग्री of the human body.
a significant fraction of the human देह is जल.
आर्थर Guyton 's Textbook of Medical physiology states that `` the कुल amount of water in a man of average weight ( 70 kilograms ) is लगभग 40 लीटर, averaging 57 प्रतिशत of his total body वज़न.
in a नवजात शिशु, this may be as ऊँची as 75 प्रतिशत of the देह weight, but it progressively decreases from जनम to old age, सबसे of the घटी occurring during the पहला 10 years of life.
Also, मोटापा decreases the प्रतिशत of जल in the देह, sometimes to as low as 45 प्रतिशत ''.
These आंकड़े हैं statistical averages, so हैं illustrative, और like सब biostatistics, होगा vary साथ बाते like प्रकार of जनसांख्यिकी, age and क्रमांक of लोगों sampled, और methodology.
so there is नहीं, और can नहीं be, a फिगर कि is exactly the वही लिये सब लोगों, लिये इस or कोई other physiological माप.
लिये उदाहरण, Jackson 's ( 1985 ) Anatomy & Physiology लिये नर्स देता a फिगर of 60 % for the proportion of body-weight attributable to जल, which approximates guyton 's 57 %.
in diseased राज्य जहाँ body water is प्रभावित, the कम्पार्टमेंट or compartments कि have changed can give clues to the nature of the problem.
देह water is regulated by हार्मोन, including anti-diuretic हार्मोन ( अध ), aldosterone और अलिंदी natriuretic पेप्टाइड.
प्रति netter 's एटलस of इंसान physiology, body जल is टूटा down into the following compartments:
Intracellular fluid ( 2/3 of body जल ).
Per Guyton, in a body containing 40 लीटर of fluid, परिचय 25 लीटर is intracellular, which amounts to 62.5 % ( 5/8 ), बंद पर्याप्त to the 2/3 rule of thumb.
Jackson 's ग्रन्थ राज्य 70 % of देह fluid is intracellular.
Extracellular fluid ( 1/3 of देह water ).
Per guyton 's उदाहरण, लिये a 40 लीटर body, परिचय 15 litres is extracellular, जिससे amounts to 37.5 % again, इस is बंद to the 1/3 rule of अंगूठा cited here.
प्लाज्मा ( 1/5 of extracellular fluid ).
Per Guyton 's illustration, of the 15 लीटर of extracellular द्रव, प्लाज्मा आवाज़ averages 3 लीटर.
इस amounts to 20 %, the वही as प्रति Netter 's एटलस.
अंतरालीय द्रव ( 4/5 of extracellular fluid )
transcellular द्रव ( a.k.a. `` तीसरा स्पेस, '' सामान्यतः उपेक्षित in calculations )
Contained अंदर organs, ऐसे as the जठरांत्र, cerebrospinal, peritoneal, और ocular fluids.
Self-esteem is a term प्रयुक्त in psychology to प्रतिबिंबित a person 's overall emotional evaluation of उसके or उसके अपना लायक.
It is a निर्णय of oneself as खूब as an रवैया toward the self.
Self-esteem encompasses beliefs ( लिये उदाहरण, `` i am competent, '' `` I am worthy '' ) और भाव ऐसे as triumph, despair, अभिमान and shame.
स्मिथ और Mackie define it by saying `` the self-concept is what we सोचो about the स्वः ; self-esteem, is the धनात्मक or ऋणात्मक evaluations of the self, as in कैसा we feel परिचय it. ''
self-esteem is भी ज्ञात as the evaluative आयाम of the स्वः कि includes जज्बात of worthiness, prides और discouragement.
One 's self-esteem is also closely संबद्ध साथ self-consciousness.
self-esteem is a disposition that a person रै which represents उनके निर्णयों of उनके अपना worthiness.
in the mid-1960s, मॉरिस rosenberg and social-learning पैरोकार पारिभाषित self-esteem as a personal लायक or worthiness.
nathaniel branden in 1969 पारिभाषित self-esteem as `` the experience of being competent to cope साथ the मौलिक challenges of life and होने worthy of सुख. ''
According to Branden, self-esteem is the योग of self-confidence ( a अहसास of निजी क्षमता ) and self-respect ( a feeling of निजी worth ).
it exists as a consequence of the implicit निर्णय कि every व्यक्ति रै of उनके ability to फेस जीवन 's चुनौतियां, to understand और solve समस्याएं, and उनके सही to achieve सुख, और be दिए आदर.
as a सोशल मनोवैज्ञानिक construct, self-esteem is attractive because शोधकर्ताओं have conceptualized it as an influential predictor of प्रासंगिक outcomes, ऐसे as academic achievement ( Marsh 1990 ) or exercise बर्ताव ( hagger et al. 1998 ).
in जोड, self-esteem रै also महरूम treated as an important निष्कर्ष due to इसके बंद संबंध with मनोवैज्ञानिक well-being ( दलदल 1989 ).
Self-esteem can apply specifically to a particular आयाम ( लिये उदाहरण, `` i मानना i am a good writer और i महसूस happy about कि '' ) or a वैश्विक extent ( लिये उदाहरण, `` i believe I am a ख़राब person, and feel bad about खुद in सामान्य '' ).
psychologists usually लिहाज़ self-esteem as an enduring personality characteristic ( `` trait '' self-esteem ), though सामान्य, short-term variations ( `` राज्य '' self-esteem ) also मौजूद.
Synonyms or near-synonyms of self-esteem शामिल : self-worth, self-regard, self-respect, and self-integrity.
A masonic आवास, प्रायः termed a Private आवास or constituent आवास, is the मौलिक organisational unit of freemasonry.
प्रत्येक नई आवास जरूर be warranted or चार्टर्ड by a ग्रैंड Lodge, लकिन is subject to इसके direction तभी in enforcing the प्रकाशित संविधान of the jurisdiction.
by एक्सेप्शन the तीन surviving lodges कि formed the संसार 's पहला known ग्रैंड Lodge in London ( today पुकारा the संयुक्त ग्रैंड आवास of इंग्लैण्ड ) have the अद्वितीय privilege to operate as समय immemorial i.e. बगैर ऐसे वारंट ; only एक अन्य lodge operates without a warrant - इस is the Grand stewards ' आवास in लंदन, although it is not भी entitled to the `` समय immemorial '' शीर्षक.
A Freemason is generally entitled to विज़िट any आवास, in कोई jurisdiction ( i.e. अंतर्गत कोई ग्रैंड आवास ) in amity with उसके अपना.
In कुछ jurisdictions इस privilege is प्रतिबंधित to निपुण masons ( कि is, Freemasons जो have attained the Order 's third उपाधि ).
he is पहला usually जरूरी to जाँच, and certify, the नियमितता of the संबंध of the Lodge - and be able to satisfy कि Lodge of उसके नियमितता of membership.
freemasons एकत्रित साथ as a Lodge to कार्य the three basic डिग्री of Entered Apprentice, Fellowcraft और Master Mason.

A quotation is the repetition of एक अभिव्यक्ति as भाग of another एक, विशेषकर जब the quoted अभिव्यक्ति is well-known or explicitly attributed by citation to इसके original सोर्स, and it is indicated by ( punctuated साथ ) quotation marks.
a quotation can भी refer to the repeated उपयोग of इकाई of कोई other form of अभिव्यक्ति, विशेषकर भाग of कलाकारी works : elements of a painting, दृश्यों इससे a फिल्म or भाग इससे a musical संयोजन.

ब्लैक pepper ( Piper nigrum ) is a flowering बेल in the family piperaceae, cultivated लिये इसके फल, जिससे is usually dried और प्रयुक्त as a spice और seasoning.
The fruit, known as a peppercorn when dried, is लगभग in व्यास, अंधेरा red जब fully वयस्क, और, like सब drupes, contains a single बीज.
peppercorns, और the मैदान pepper derived from उन्हें, may be वर्णित बस as pepper, or अधिक precisely as ब्लैक pepper ( पकाया and सूखी unripe फल ), ग्रीन pepper ( सूखी unripe fruit ) और श्वेत pepper ( dried पके seeds ).
Black pepper is देशी to दक्षिण इण्डिया, और is extensively cultivated वहीँ and elsewhere in तीव्र regions.
फिलहाल Vietnam is the world 's largest producer और exporter of pepper, producing 34 % of the world 's Piper nigrum क्रॉप as of 2008.
सूखी ground pepper रै महरूम प्रयुक्त since प्राचीनता for दोनो its फ्लेवर and as a medicine.
ब्लैक pepper is the संसार 's सबसे traded मसाला.
It is एक of the most आम मसाले added to यूरोपीय भोजन और इसके descendants.
the spiciness of ब्लैक pepper is due to the रासायनिक piperine, नहीं to be उलझन with the capsaicin that gives fleshy मिर्च theirs.
it is in the modern world, often युग्म साथ नमक.

a fire hydrant ( also ज्ञात colloquially as a आग प्लग in the संयुक्त राज्य or as a johnny पंप in New York नगर ), is an क्रियाशील fire सुरक्षा माप, और a source of जल provided in most शहरी, suburban और ग्रामीण क्षेत्रों साथ municipal water सेवा to enable अग्निशमन to tap into the नगरपालिका water सप्लाई to assist in extinguishing a आग.
इमारतें निकट a hydrant may qualify लिये an बीमे discount चूंकि अग्निशमन चाहिए be समर्थ to अधिक rapidly बुझा a fire on the insured प्रॉपर्टी.
the concept of आग plugs तिथियाँ to at least the 17th सदी.
This was a समय जब अग्निशमन responding to a कॉल होता खुदाई down to the लकड़ी water मेन्स और hastily bore a छेद to सुरक्षित water to लड़ो fires.
The जल would भरण the hole creating a अस्थाई well, और be transported from the खूब to the fire by बाल्टी brigades or, बाद, by hand-pumped आग इंजन.
The holes यहूद तब plugged साथ stoppers, सामान्यतः redwood, which over time came to be ज्ञात as आग plugs.
the स्थान of the प्लग would प्रायः be recorded or चिह्नित so that it could be reused in भविष्य फ़ायर.
This is the सोर्स of the colloquial पद आग प्लग still प्रयुक्त लिये fire hydrants today.
After the ग्रेट Fire of लंदन in 1666, the city संस्थापित जल mains साथ छेद drilled at intervals, equipped साथ risers, allowing an अभिगम point to the लकड़ी आग plugs इससे गली level.
the invention of a post- or pillar-type fire hydrant is generally credited to Frederick graff Sr., मुख्य इंजीनियर of the Philadelphia Water Works around the साल 1801.
it था a combination hose/faucet आउटलेट and थी of `` wet barrel '' डिज़ाइन with the valve in the top.
It is said कि Graff आयोजित the पहला पेटेंट लिये a आग hydrant, but this can not be verified क्युकी the पेटेंट दफ्तर in वॉशिंगटन D.C. caught on आग in 1836 destroying अनेक पेटेंट records इससे that period in the process.
The अध्यक्ष of the गणतंत्र of South Africa is the सिर of state और head of सरकारी अंतर्गत South Africa 's संविधान.
इससे 1961 to 1994, the सिर of राज्य was पुकारा the राज्य President.
the President is निर्वाचित by सदस्यों of the नेशनल सभा, the निम्नतर हाउस of पार्लियामेंट, and is प्रायः the नेता of the largest party, which has been the अफ़्रीकी नेशनल कॉंग्रेस चूंकि the first non-racial elections यहूद held on 27 अप्रैल 1994.
The भूमिका थी originally founded to be पृथक from the now defunct भूमिका of prime minister, but the दो भूमिकाएँ were merged in the 1983 संविधान which specified a four-year पद of दफ्तर.

Under the अंतरिम संविधान ( मान्य इससे 1994 to 1996 ), वहीँ was a सरकारी of National Unity, in जिससे an mp इससे the largest opposition पार्टी थी entitled to a स्थिति as डिप्टी President.
साथ साथ Thabo mbeki, the पिछला State अध्यक्ष, f.w. de klerk also परोसा as डिप्टी अध्यक्ष, in उसके क्षमता as the leader of the नेशनल पार्टी जिससे थी the second-largest पार्टी in the नई Parliament.

खास education or खास needs education is the शिक्षा of विद्यार्थी साथ खास needs in a रास्ता कि addresses the students ' व्यक्तिगत differences और needs.
Ideally, इस process involves the individually नियोजित और systematically monitored व्यवस्था of शिक्षण procedures, adapted उपकरण और सामग्री, accessible settings, and other interventions designed to सहायता learners साथ special needs achieve a उच्चतर level of निजी self-sufficiency and कामयाबी in स्कूल and जातियाँ than होता be available if the छात्र यहूद तभी दिए access to a ठेठ कक्षा शिक्षा.
Common खास needs include challenges साथ learning, संचार challenges, emotional और behavioral विकार, physical disabilities, और developmental विकार.
Students साथ ये kinds of खास needs हैं संभावित to लाभ इससे additional शैक्षणिक services such as अलग approaches to teaching, use of प्रौद्योगिकी, a specifically adapted शिक्षण क्षेत्रफल, or resource room.
बौद्धिक giftedness is a अंतर in learning और can भी benefit from specialized teaching तकनीकों or different educational कार्यक्रम, लकिन the पद `` special शिक्षा '' is generally प्रयुक्त to specifically indicate instruction of students whose खास needs reduce उनके ability to सीख independently or in an ordinary classroom, और gifted शिक्षा is handled separately.
in सबसे विकसित देशों, educators हैं modifying teaching methods और environments so that the maximum number of विद्यार्थी are served in general शिक्षा environments.
खास education in विकसित देशों is often regarded less as a `` प्लेस '' and अधिक as `` a दायरा of सेवाएं, उपलब्धियाँ in every स्कूल. ''
संयोजन can reduce सोशल stigmas और improve academic achievement for अनेक विद्यार्थी.
the opposite of खास शिक्षा is general शिक्षा.
General शिक्षा is the standard curriculum presented with मानक teaching विधि और बगैर अतिरिक्त supports.

He निभाई a significant भूमिका in the peaceful transition from communism to capitalism in हंगेरियाई ( 1984–89 ) और provided एक of Europe 's largest उच्चतर education endowments to सेंट्रल यूरोपीय University in बुडापेस्ट.

an कर्ता portraying सिकंदर ग्राहम Bell बोलना into an जल्दी मॉडल telephone.
The invention of the telephone is the culmination of work done by अनेक individuals, the इतिहास of जिससे involves a संग्रहण of दावा and counterclaims.
The development of the modern विद्युत टेलीफोन शामिल an सरणी of lawsuits संस्थापित upon the पेटेंट दावा of several individuals और numerous कंपनियाँ.

a निपुण of ठीक कला ( mfa, m.f.a. ) is a ग्रैजुएट उपाधि typically requiring 2–3 सालो of postgraduate study beyond the स्नातक 's degree ( bfa ), although the पद of पढ़ाई होगा vary by देश or by विश्वविद्यालयों.
The MFA is a creative उपाधि प्रायः awarded as a terminal degree in visual कला, रचनात्मक लिखने, filmmaking, नृत्य, or थिएटर और अन्य performing arts.
coursework is primarily of an लागू or performing nature with the program often culminating in a प्रमुख work or प्रदर्शन.
निपुण of ठीक Arts कार्यक्रम have generally जरूरी a bachelor 's degree prior to admission, लकिन many do not require कि the undergraduate प्रमुख be the same as the MFA फ़ील्ड of study.
the सबसे important admissions requirement रै प्रायः महरूम a sample पोर्टफोलियो or a performance ऑडिशन.
the Master of Fine कला differs इससे the निपुण of कला in कि the mfa, जबकि an अकादमिक program, centers around अभ्यास in the particular field, whereas कार्यक्रम अग्रणी to the ma usually center on the scholarly, अकादमिक, or नाजुक study of the फ़ील्ड.
additionally, in the संयुक्त States, an mfa is पहचाना as a terminal उपाधि for practitioners of Visual Art, डिज़ाइन, नृत्य, थिएटर, film/video, New Media, and रचनात्मक लिखने - अर्थ कि it is considered to be the उच्चतम उपाधि in इसके फ़ील्ड, और is प्रयुक्त as a न्यूनतम योग्यता to be able to लागू to become a Full-Time Professor शिक्षण at the विश्वविद्यालयों स्तर in these disciplines.
वहीँ are अपवाद to इस standard in the Arts, notably in the case of music प्रदर्शन, जहाँ the mfa is नहीं seen as a टर्मिनल degree in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of the more standardized dma degree.
it is also critical to नोट कि in the ब्याज of extending the कनेक्शन between रचनात्मक production और जारी academic research, some universities have स्थापित practice-based Ph.D कार्यक्रम in fields such as रचनात्मक writing, visual कला, नई मीडिया, डिज़ाइन and theater.
While इस रै had an प्रभाव in रचनात्मक लिखने, and to a lesser extent in design और new मीडिया, the influx of graduates इससे practice-based PhD कार्यक्रम रै not appreciably बदला the standard लिये the MFA as the टर्मिनल degree in सबसे कला disciplines yet.
This is an जारी contentious topic, और is the बारंबार विषय of academic panels, विशेषकर at the सालाना College आर्ट संघ सम्मेलन.
the CAA 2008 दिशानिर्देश regarding the mfa strongly re-affirms that the phd is not जरूरी as a टर्मिनल degree in the विज़ुअल arts.
The परमाणु bombings of the शहरों of हिरोशिमा and Nagasaki in Japan were conducted by the United States दौरान the फाइनल stages of World युद्ध ii in 1945.
the दो events are the only उपयोग of nuclear हथियार in युद्ध to date.
Following a firebombing अभियान कि नष्ट अनेक जापानी शहरों, the Allies prepared लिये a costly आक्रमण of Japan.
The युद्ध in यूरोपीय ended when नाजी Germany signed इसके instrument of surrender on 8 May, लकिन the प्रशांत युद्ध जारी.
साथ साथ the United किंगडम and the Republic of चीन, the United राज्य called लिये a surrender of जापानी in the Potsdam घोषणा on 26 जुलाई 1945, threatening जापानी साथ `` prompt और utter destruction ''.
the जापानी सरकारी उपेक्षित इस ultimatum, और the United States तैनात दो नाभिकीय weapons developed by the मैनहटन Project.
अमरीकी airmen dropped Little लड़के on the city of Hiroshima on 6 August 1945, followed by मोटे man over Nagasaki on 9 अगस्त.
भीतर the first दो to four महीने of the bombings, the acute effects killed 90,000–166,000 people in हिरोशिमा और 60,000–80,000 in नागासाकी, with roughly half of the मौतों in प्रत्येक नगर occurring on the first दिन.
the हिरोशिमा prefecture health विभाग अनुमानित कि, of the लोगों जो died on the दिन of the explosion, 60 % died इससे फ्लैश or flame burns, 30 % इससे गिरना मलबा and 10 % from अन्य causes.
दौरान the following महीने, विशाल संख्याएँ died from the effect of burns, radiation sickness, और other चोटों, compounded by illness.
in a US अनुमान of the कुल immediate and छोटी term कारण of मौत, 15–20 % died इससे विकिरण बीमारी, 20–30 % from burns, and 50–60 % from अन्य चोटों, compounded by बीमारी.
In दोनो cities, सबसे of the मुर्दे यहूद नागरिकों, although Hiroshima था a sizeable गैरीसन.
on 15 अगस्त, six दिनों after the bombing of नागासाकी, Japan घोषित इसके surrender to the allies, signing the Instrument of आत्मसमर्पण on 2 September, officially ending संसार युद्ध ii.
the bombings led, in part, to post-war जापानी 's adopting तीन non-nuclear सिद्धान्त, forbidding the स्वदेश from nuclear armament.
the भूमिका of the bombings in Japan 's आत्मसमर्पण and their ethical औचित्य are still debated.
Mohandas करमचंद Gandhi ( ; 2 October 1869 – 30 जनवरी 1948 ), commonly known as महात्मा Gandhi, थी the preeminent leader of भारतीय राष्ट्रवाद in British-ruled India.
Employing non-violent सिविल disobedience, गांधी led India to स्वतंत्रता और प्रेरित आंदोलनों लिये non-violence, सिविल rights and freedom across the संसार.
The son of a वरिष्ठ सरकारी official, गांधी was born and raised in a Hindu Bania community in coastal Gujarat, and trained in law in London.
गांधी became प्रसिद्ध by fighting for the सिविल अधिकारों of Muslim और हिन्दू Indians in South Africa, using new techniques of non-violent civil disobedience that he विकसित.
returning to इण्डिया in 1915, he नियत about organising peasants to विरोध excessive land-taxes.
a lifelong opponent of `` communalism `` ( i.e. basing politics on religion ) he reached आउट widely to all धार्मिक समूह.
He became a नेता of मुसलमान protesting the declining status of the Caliphate.
assuming नेतृत्व of the भारतीय नेशनल Congress in 1921, Gandhi led देशभर अभियान लिये easing गरीबी, expanding women 's अधिकारों, भवन religious and ethnic सौहार्द, समाप्ति untouchability, increasing आर्थिक self-reliance, और ऊपर all लिये achieving स्वराज —the independence of इण्डिया इससे British हुकूमत.
Gandhi led इंडियंस in protesting the नेशनल salt कर with the Dandi Salt कूच in 1930, और बाद in demanding the अंग्रेजों to immediately Quit इण्डिया in 1942, दौरान संसार War ii.
He थी imprisoned लिये that और for numerous अन्य राजनैतिक offenses over the years.
गांधी sought to practice non-violence और सच्चाई in all situations, और advocated that अन्य do the वही.
he saw the गांवों as the कोर of the सच्चा इण्डिया and promoted self-sufficiency ; he किया not support the industrialization programs of उसके शिष्य जवाहरलाल नेहरू.
he जिया modestly in a self-sufficient आवासीय जातियाँ और wore the परंपरागत Indian dhoti और चादर, woven with धागे he था हाथ spun on a charkha.
उसके मुख्य राजनैतिक दुश्मन in ब्रिटेन थी विंस्टन Churchill, who ridiculed him as a `` half-naked फकीर. ''
he थी a dedicated vegetarian, और undertook long fasts as means of दोनो self-purification और राजनैतिक mobilization.
In उसके पिछला year, अप्रसन्न at the विभाजन of इण्डिया, Gandhi worked to रोकें the carnage between मुसलमान, हिन्दुओं और सिखों that raged in the किनारा क्षेत्रफल between India and Pakistan.
He थी assassinated on 30 January 1948 by nathuram गोडसे जो विचार गांधी थी too सहानुभूतिपूर्ण to इण्डिया 's Muslims.
30 January is observed as शहीदो ' Day in India.
the honorific Mahatma ( `` ग्रेट Soul '' ) was लागू to him by 1914.
in इण्डिया he was भी पुकारा Bapu ( `` पिता '' ).
He is ज्ञात in इण्डिया as the Father of the स्वदेश ; his birthday, 2 October, is commemorated there as गांधी Jayanti, a national अवकाश, और world-wide as the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Day of Non-Violence.
Gandhi 's philosophy थी not theoretical लकिन one of pragmatism, कि is, practicing उसके सिद्धान्त in the पल.
पूछा to दे a संदेश to the people, he होता respond, `` My जीवन is my संदेश. ''
जोन Crawford ( March 23, ca. 1904 – May 10, 1977 ), born lucille fay lesueur, was an अमरीकी actress in film, television and थिएटर.
starting as a नर्तकी in traveling नाट्य companies पहले debuting on ब्रॉडवे, Crawford was signed to a गति चित्र contract by metro-goldwyn-mayer in 1925.
Initially कुंठित by the आकार and विशेषता of उसके भाग, क्रॉफर्ड began a campaign of self-publicity and became nationally ज्ञात as a flapper by the end of the 1920s.
In the 1930s, क्रॉफर्ड 's कीर्ति rivaled, और बाद outlasted, MGM सहयोगियों norma Shearer और greta Garbo.
Crawford often played मेहनती young महिलाओं जो ढूँढें romance और financial कामयाबी.
ये `` rags-to-riches '' कहानियां were well प्राप्त by Depression -era ऑडियंस and यहूद popular with women.
क्रॉफर्ड became एक of हॉलीवुड 's सबसे prominent फिल्म सितारों और एक of the उच्चतम सशुल्क महिलाओं in the United States, लकिन her films began खोने धन और by the end of the 1930s वो थी labeled `` box office ज़हर ''.
बाद an अनुपस्थिति of nearly two years इससे the स्क्रीन, क्रॉफर्ड staged a comeback by starring in मिल्ड्रेड Pierce ( 1945 ), लिये which वो जीती the अकादमी पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन Actress.
in 1955, वो became involved साथ the pepsi-cola कम्पनी through उसके विवाह to company Chairman Alfred Steele.
बाद उसके death in 1959, Crawford was elected to भरण his रिक्ति on the board of निर्देशकों but थी forcibly रिटायर्ड in 1973.
वो जारी एक्टिंग in फिल्मी और टेलीविज़न regularly through the 1960s, when उसके performances became fewer ; after the रिलीज of the अंग्रेजों horror फिल्मी Trog in 1970, Crawford रिटायर्ड इससे the screen.
following a पब्लिक रूप in 1974, after जिससे unflattering छायाचित्र were प्रकाशित, क्रॉफर्ड withdrew from public life और became increasingly reclusive जबतक उसके मौत in 1977.
क्रॉफर्ड married four times.
Her पहला तीन marriages ended in divorce ; the पिछला ended with the death of husband Alfred Steele.
वो adopted पाँच children, one of whom थी reclaimed by उसके जनम माँ.
क्रॉफर्ड 's relationships with her two पुरानी children, क्रिस्टीना and क्रिस्टोफर, यहूद acrimonious.
क्रॉफर्ड disinherited the दो और, after क्रॉफर्ड 's मौत, Christina लिखा a `` tell-all '' संस्मरण, mommie dearest, in जिससे she कथित a lifelong पैटर्न of physical and emotional गाली perpetrated by Crawford.
वो थी voted the दसवाँ greatest मादा star in the history of अमरीकी cinema by the American फिल्मी संस्थान.

Tonneau कवर ( or ) describes a मुश्किल or नरम कवर प्रयुक्त to protect unoccupied यात्री seats in a convertible or roadster, or the cargo bed in a pickup ट्रक.
मुश्किल tonneau कवर खोलें by a hinging or फोल्डिंग यांत्रिकी जबकि नरम कवर open by rolling up.
The tonneau कवर is प्रयुक्त to छिपाते कार्गो.
जब the cover is खींचा out, it keeps वस्तुएं out of the सूर्य और provides अतिरिक्त security by keeping personal वस्तुएं आउट of sight, as खूब as shielding the driver इससे दृश्य.
ट्विटर is an ऑनलाइन सोशल नेटवर्किंग सेवा और microblogging सेवा कि enables its उपयोक्ता to भेजें और पढ़ा text-based संदेश of up to 140 वर्ण, known as `` tweets ''.
ट्विटर was created in March 2006 by जोकर dorsey और by जुलाई, the सोशल networking साईट was launched.
The service rapidly gained विश्वव्यापी popularity, साथ over 500 million पंजीकृत उपयोक्ता as of 2012, generating over 340 million tweets daily और हैंडलिंग over 1.6 अरब ढूंढें queries प्रति दिन.
चूंकि इसके लॉन्च, Twitter रै become एक of the टेन सबसे visited वेबसाइटों on the अंतरजाल, और रै महरूम described as `` the SMS of the अंतरजाल. ''
अपंजीकृत उपयोक्ता can पढ़ा tweets, जबकि पंजीकृत users can पोस्ट tweets through the website interface, sms, or a दायरा of apps लिये मोबाईल devices.
Twitter Inc. is आधारित in सैन फ्रांसिस्को, साथ additional servers और कार्यालयों in नई York नगर, बोस्टन, और सैन अंतोनियो.
the Hangover is a 2009 अमरीकी कॉमेडी फिल्मी, co-produced and निर्देशित by टॉड Phillips और written by Jon Lucas and Scott Moore.
it is the पहला फिल्मी of the hangover मताधिकार.the फिल्मी stars ब्राडली Cooper, ed Helms, zach galifianakis, हीथर ग्राहम, जस्टिन bartha, and जेफरी Tambor.
the hangover tells the story of फिल Wenneck, stu दाम और Alan गार्नर, जो travel to Las Vegas लिये a स्नातक party to celebrate their dost डग Billings ' impending विवाह.
however, फिल, stu and Alan have no मेमोरी of the पिछला रात्रि 's कार्यक्रम और जरूर ढूँढें डग पहले the विवाह can लो place.
Lucas और मूर wrote the स्क्रिप्ट बाद कार्यपालिका producer Chris Bender 's dost disappeared and had a विशाल विधेयक बाद being भेजा to a स्ट्रिप क्लबों.
बाद Lucas और मूर sold it to the studio लिये $ 2 million, फिलिप्स और जेरेमी garelick rewrote the स्क्रिप्ट to शामिल a tiger as well as a subplot involving a baby और a पुलिस क्रूजर, and also सहित boxer Mike टायसन.
फिल्मांकन took प्लेस in Nevada लिये 15 days, और during फिल्मांकन, the तीन प्रमुख actors ( Cooper, Helms और galifianakis ) formed a दोस्ती.
the hangover was released on June 5, 2009, बनने a नाजुक और commercial कामयाबी.
it became the tenth-highest-grossing film of 2009, with a विश्वव्यापी gross of over US $ 467 लाख.
आलोचकों praised the फिल्मी 's comedic approach लकिन criticized it लिये इसके vulgarity.
The film जीती the सुनहरी ग्लोब पुरस्कार लिये Best गति चित्र – Musical or कॉमेडी, and प्राप्त अनेक other accolades.
It is the tenth-highest-grossing फिल्मी of 2009 in the संसार, as well as the दूसरी highest-grossing r-rated कॉमेडी ever in the United States, surpassing a रिकार्ड previously आयोजित by बेवर्ली Hills cop लिये almost 25 years और बाद होने surpassed by टेड in 2012.
आउट of सब r-rated films, it is the तीसरा highest-grossing ever in the u.S., behind तभी the जुनून of the Christ and the मेट्रिक्स reloaded.
a sequel, The hangover Part ii, was released in 2011, and a तीसरा and final फिल्मी, the hangover भाग iii, is नियत लिये release in 2013.
कार्यक्रम involving meiosis, प्रर्दशित chromosomal क्रॉसओवर
meiosis ( ) is a खास type of cell division necessary for यौन reproduction in eukaryotes.
the cells उत्पादित by meiosis are gametes or spores.
in many जीवों, सहित सब animals और जमीन plants ( but not कुछ other समूह such as fungi ), गैमीट हैं पुकारा sperm और अंडा कोशिकाएं.
Whilst the प्रक्रम of meiosis bears a number of similarities साथ the 'life-cycle ' कोशिका division process of mitosis, it differs in two महत्वपूर्ण आदरs:
the गुणसूत्रों in meiosis undergo a recombination which shuffles the genes producing a अलग जेनेटिक combination in प्रत्येक gamete, compared साथ the co-existence of प्रत्येक of the दो पृथक pairs of प्रत्येक chromosome ( एक प्राप्त इससे प्रत्येक जनक ) in each कोशिका जिससे परिणाम इससे mitosis.
the निष्कर्ष of meiosis is potentially चार ( genetically unique ) अगुणित cells, compared with the two ( genetically identical ) द्विगुणित कोशिकाएं उत्पादित from mitosis.
Meiosis begins साथ एक diploid कोशिका containing दो नक़ल of प्रत्येक chromosome —one इससे the सजीव 's माँ और एक इससे इसके पिता.
the cell divides twice, potentially producing up to चार अगुणित cells containing one नक़ल of प्रत्येक chromosome.
( `` Potentially '' because in some मामले, ऐसे as the गठन of oocytes in mammals, only एक of the संभावित four haploid कोशिकाएं survives. )
in पशु the अगुणित cell resulting from meiosis is a पुरूष or मादा gamete.
Each of the resulting गुणसूत्रों in the gamete cells is a अद्वितीय mixture of maternal और पैतृक DNA, resulting in औलाद कि हैं genetically पृथक इससे either जनक.
This देता rise to genetic विविधता in sexually reproducing populations.
इस जेनेटिक विविधता can provide the variation of शारीरिक और behavioural गुण ( phenotypes ) upon जिससे प्राकृतिक selection can act, लकिन, as described below in Section 6, Origin और फलन of meiosis, the genetic diversity may be largely a by-product of the समजात recombination कि is primarily employed लिये its DNA repair function during meiosis.
it is भी noteworthy कि दौरान meiosis, विशिष्ट जीनों हैं more अत्यधिक transcribed, and ये हैं पुकारा the meiome, the पद used in functional genomics लिये the meiotic transcriptome.
Meiosis is a कुंजी विशेषता for all sexually reproducing eukaryotes in which समजात chromosome pairing, synapse और recombination occur.
in addition to strong meiotic stage-specific अभिव्यक्ति of mrna ( the meiome ), however, there are भी pervasive translational controls ( e.g. selective usage of preformed mRNA ), regulating the ultimate meiotic stage-specific protein अभिव्यक्ति of जीनों दौरान meiosis.
यूँ, दोनो the meiome and translational नियंत्रण determine the व्यापक restructuring of meiotic cells needed to carry आउट meiosis.
Prior to the meiosis प्रक्रम the कोशिका 's गुणसूत्रों are duplicated by a गोलाकार of डीएनए replication, बनाना इससे the मातृ and पैतृक संस्करण of each chromosome ( homologs ) दो exact नक़ल, सिस्टर chromatids, attached at the centromere region.
in the शुरूआत of meiosis the मातृ and पैतृक homologs pair to प्रत्येक other.
तब वे typically एक्सचेंज भाग by समजात recombination leading to crossovers of डीएनए between the मातृ और paternal संस्करण of the chromosome.
Spindle fibers bind to the centromeres of प्रत्येक जोड़ी of homologs और arrange the pairs at the spindle equator.
तब the fibers खींचो the recombined homologs to opposite poles of the cell.
as the chromosomes मूव दूर from the center the कोशिका divides into two बेटी कोशिकाएं, प्रत्येक containing a अगुणित क्रमांक of गुणसूत्रों रचित of two chromatids.
After the recombined maternal और पैतृक homologs have अलग into the दो daughter कोशिकाएं, a दूसरी गोलाकार of कोशिका division occurs.
वहीँ meiosis ends as the दो sister chromatids making up प्रत्येक homolog हैं separated और move into one of the चार resulting gamete कोशिकाएं.
Upon fertilization, लिये example when a sperm enters an egg cell, दो gamete cells produced by meiosis fuse.
the gamete from the mother और the gamete from the पिता प्रत्येक contribute एक हाफ of the set of chromosomes that मेक up the new औलाद 's genome.
Meiosis uses अनेक of the same mechanisms as समसूत्रण, a प्रकार of cell प्रभाग used by eukaryotes जैसे plants and पशु to split एक कोशिका into दो identical daughter cells.
In all पौधे और in अनेक protists meiosis results in the गठन of बीजाणुओं : अगुणित cells that can divide vegetatively without undergoing fertilization.
मुक्केबाज़ी ( pugilism, prize लड़, the sweet विज्ञान or in यूनानी pygmachia ) is a martial art and combat sport in which दो people engage in a प्रतियोगिता of शक्ति, speed, reflexes, सहनशीलता और होगा by फेंकना punches साथ gloved hands.
amateur मुक्केबाज़ी is an ओलम्पिक and Commonwealth खेल and is a common fixture in सबसे of the प्रमुख अंतरराष्ट्रीय खेल - it भी has इसके own World Championships.
मुक्केबाज़ी is पर्यवेक्षित by a रेफरी over a series of one- to three-minute intervals पुकारा rounds.
the result is decided जब an प्रतिद्वन्दी is deemed incapable to continue by a रेफरी, is disqualified for तोड़कर a नियम, resigns by फेंकना in a तौलिया, or is सुनाया the विजेता or हारा based on the judges ' scorecards at the समाप्त of the contest.
The जनम घंटा of मुक्केबाज़ी as a sport may be इसके स्वीकृति by the प्राचीन यूनानियों as an ओलम्पिक game as जल्दी as 688 BC.
मुक्केबाज़ी विकसित from 16th- और 18th-century prizefights, largely in Great ब्रिटेन, to the forerunner of modern मुक्केबाज़ी in the mid-19th century, again initially in Great Britain और बाद in the संयुक्त राज्य.
In 2004, ESPN क्रमित boxing as the most मुश्किल sport in the संसार.
Agreement or concord happens जब a शब्द changes form depending on the अन्य शब्द to जिससे it relates.
it is an उदाहरण of inflection, और प्रायः involves making the मान of some grammatical category ( such as gender or व्यक्ति ) `` सहमत '' between different words or भाग of the वाक्य.
लिये उदाहरण, in Standard English, एक may कह i am or he is, लकिन नहीं `` i is '' or `` he am ''.
This is क्युकी the grammar of the भाषा requires that the verb और इसके subject सहमत in व्यक्ति.
the pronouns I and he are पहला and third person क्रमशः, as हैं the क्रिया forms am और is.
the क्रिया रूप जरूर be चयनित so कि it has the same व्यक्ति as the विषय.
the अनुबंध आधारित on overt grammatical categories as above is औपचारिक अनुबंध, in कंट्रास्ट to notional अनुबंध, जिससे is आधारित on अर्थ.
लिये उदाहरण, the phrase the संयुक्त States is treated as एकवचन लिये उद्देश्य of agreement, भी हालांकि it is formally बहुवचन.

A lawyer, according to Black 's विधि शब्दकोष, is `` a person learned in the विधि ; as an attorney, counsel or solicitor ; a person जो is practicing विधि. ''
विधि is the प्रणाली of नियम of conduct स्थापित by the sovereign सरकारी of a society to सही wrongs, maintain the stability of political और सोशल प्राधिकार, and उद्धार इंसाफ.
working as a lawyer involves the व्यावहारिक application of अमूर्त विधिक theories और ज्ञान to solve विशिष्ट individualized समस्याएं, or to अग्रिम the रूचि of those जो retain ( i.e., hire ) वकील to perform विधिक सेवाएं.
the भूमिका of the lawyer varies significantly आरपार legal jurisdictions, and so it can be treated यहाँ in तभी the सबसे general शर्तें.

the Family और Medical छोड़ अधिनियम of 1993 ( FMLA ) is a संयुक्त राज्य federal विधि requiring covered नियोक्ता to provide कर्मचारी job-protected and unpaid छोड़ for qualified medical and family reasons.
Qualified चिकित्सा and परिवार reasons शामिल : निजी or परिवार बीमारी, family सैन्य छोड़, pregnancy, अपनाना, or the foster care placement of a चाइल्ड.
the FMLA is administered by the मजदूरी and घंटा Division of the संयुक्त राज्य विभाग of मजदूर.
the bill was a प्रमुख भाग of President विधेयक क्लिंटन 's कार्यसूची in his first term.
अध्यक्ष क्लिंटन हस्ताक्षरित the विधेयक into विधि on February 5, 1993 ( ; 29 u.s.c. सेक. 2601 ; 29 cfr 825 ) and it took प्रभाव on अगस्त 5, 1993, छह महीने बाद.
The fmla थी intended `` to संतुलन the demands of the कार्यस्थल साथ the needs of परिवारों. ''
the Act allows योग्य कर्मचारी to लो up to 12 work weeks of unpaid छोड़ during any 12-month काल to attend to the गंभीर health कंडीशन of the कर्मचारी, जनक, spouse or चाइल्ड, or लिये pregnancy or care of a newborn child, or लिये adoption or फोस्टर care of a child.
in अनुक्रम to be योग्य for FMLA leave, an employee जरूर have been at the business at तनिक 12 months, और worked at least 1,250 घंटों over the पास्ट 12 महीने, और work at a स्थान जहाँ the कम्पनी employs 50 or अधिक कर्मचारी भीतर 75 miles.
the fmla कवर both public- and private-sector कर्मचारी, लकिन certain श्रेणी of कर्मचारी हैं excluded, सहित निर्वाचित officials and उनके निजी staff सदस्यों.
the वियतनाम युद्ध ( ) was a Cold War -era सैन्य conflict that occurred in वियतनाम, लाओस, and कंबोडिया from 1 नवम्बर 1955 to the पतन of साइगॉन on 30 अप्रैल 1975.
इस war followed the पहला Indochina युद्ध and थी लड़ा between North Vietnam, समर्थित by इसके कम्युनिस्ट allies, और the government of दक्षिण वियतनाम, समर्थित by the United राज्य and अन्य anti-communist countries.
the Viet Cong ( also ज्ञात as the नेशनल मुक्ति सामने, or nlf ), a हलके armed दक्षिण वियतनामी communist आम सामने निर्देशित by the उत्तर, largely fought a छापामार युद्ध विरूद्ध anti-communist शक्तियां in the region.
the वियतनाम लोगों 's फौज ( उत्तर Vietnamese फौज ) engaged in a more conventional war, at टाइम्स committing large इकाई into battle.
U.S. and दक्षिण वियतनामी शक्तियां relied on एयर superiority and overwhelming firepower to conduct search और नष्ट operations, involving मैदान forces, तोपखाने, और airstrikes.
The U.S. सरकारी viewed involvement in the युद्ध as a way to prevent a कम्युनिस्ट कब्ज़ा of दक्षिण Vietnam as part of their wider रणनीति of containment.
the उत्तर Vietnamese सरकारी and viet Cong यहूद लड़ to reunify Vietnam अंतर्गत communist नियम.
वे viewed the conflict as a औपनिवेशिक युद्ध, लड़ा initially विरूद्ध France, backed by the U.S., और बाद against दक्षिण Vietnam, which it regarded as a U.S. कठपुतली राज्य.
American सैन्य advisors arrived in कया थी then French इंडोचायना शुरूआत in 1950.
u.S. involvement escalated in the जल्दी 1960s, साथ troop levels tripling in 1961 and tripling again in 1962.
u.S. कॉम्बैट इकाई यहूद तैनात शुरूआत in 1965.
परिचालन spanned international सीमायें, with लाओस and कंबोडिया heavily bombed.
अमरीकी भागीदारी in the युद्ध peaked in 1968, at the time of the tet अप्रिय.
After this, U.S. ground शक्तियां were gradually withdrawn as भाग of a नीति ज्ञात as vietnamization.
despite the पेरिस सलाम accords, signed by सब पार्टियों in जनवरी 1973, fighting जारी.
u.S. सैन्य भागीदारी ended on 15 अगस्त 1973 as a परिणाम of the case–church amendment passed by the U.S. Congress.
the capture of साइगॉन by the वियतनाम लोगों 's फौज in अप्रैल 1975 marked the end of the war, and उत्तर and दक्षिण वियतनाम were reunified the following साल.
The युद्ध exacted a विशाल इंसान लागत in terms of fatalities ( देखिए Vietnam युद्ध casualties ).
Estimates of the number of Vietnamese सैनिको और नागरिकों मारे vary इससे 800,000 to 3.1 million.
कुछ 200,000–300,000 Cambodians, 20,000–200,000 Laotians, और 58,220 u.S. service members भी died in the conflict.
क्लीवलैंड ज्वालामुखी in the Aleutian आइलैंड्स of अलास्का photographed from the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Space स्टेशन, may 2006.

a ज्वालामुखी is an खोलने, or rupture, in a ग्रह 's सतह or क्रस्ट, which allows hot मैग्मा, volcanic राख और गैसों to एस्केप इससे the मैग्मा chamber below the surface.
Volcanoes are generally found जहाँ tectonic plates हैं diverging or converging.
a mid-oceanic लकीरें, लिये example the mid-atlantic Ridge, has examples of ज्वालामुखी caused by अपसारी tectonic प्लेटों pulling अलावा ; the प्रशांत Ring of आग रै उदाहरण of ज्वालामुखी caused by convergent tectonic प्लेटों coming साथ.
By कंट्रास्ट, ज्वालामुखी हैं प्रायः नहीं निर्मित जहाँ two tectonic plates स्लाइड past one another.
Volcanoes can भी form जहाँ वहीँ is stretching and thinning of the धरती 's क्रस्ट in the interiors of plates, e.g., in the ईस्ट African Rift, the Wells Gray-Clearwater volcanic फ़ील्ड और the रिओ ग्रांडे दरार in उत्तर अमेरिका.
इस प्रकार of volcanism falls अंतर्गत the छतरियाँ of `` थाली परिकल्पना '' volcanism.
Volcanism दूर इससे थाली boundaries रै भी महरूम explained as mantle plumes.
These so-called `` hotspots ``, लिये उदाहरण हवाई, हैं postulated to उठता इससे upwelling diapirs with magma इससे the core–mantle boundary, 3,000 km deep in the धरती.
erupting ज्वालामुखी can पोज़ अनेक जोखिमों, not तभी in the तात्कालिक vicinity of the eruption.
volcanic ash can be a threat to वायुयान, in particular those साथ जेट engines जहाँ राख अणु can be melted by the high operating temperature.
Large eruptions can affect तापमान as ash और droplets of sulfuric एसिड obscure the सूर्य और कूल the धरती 's lower atmosphere or troposphere ; however, they भी अवशोषित ऊष्मा radiated up इससे the धरती, thereby वार्मिंग the stratosphere.
Historically, so-called volcanic winters have caused catastrophic अकाल.

a pothole ( sometimes called a केतली and ज्ञात in भाग of the पश्चिमी United राज्य as a chuckhole ) is a प्रकार of disruption in the सतह of a roadway जहाँ a portion of the सड़क material has टूटा दूर, leaving a hole.
renal कोशिका कार्सिनोमा ( RCC, also known as hypernephroma ) is a kidney कर्कट कि originates in the lining of the proximal convoluted tubule, the बहुत small tubes in the kidney that transport gf ( glomerular filtrate ) from the glomerulus to the descending limb of the nephron.
RCC is the सबसे common type of गुर्दा कर्कट in वयस्कों, जिम्मेदार लिये approximately 80 % of cases.
it is भी ज्ञात to be the सबसे lethal of सब the genitourinary tumors.
Initial उपचार is सबसे commonly a radical or partial nephrectomy and remains the mainstay of curative treatment.
जहाँ the ट्यूमर is confined to the renal parenchyma, the 5-year survival रेट is 60-70 %, but इस is lowered considerably जहाँ metastases have स्प्रेड.
it is relatively resistant to radiation चिकित्सा और chemotherapy, although कुछ मामले respond to immunotherapy.
targeted कर्कट therapies ऐसे as sunitinib, temsirolimus, bevacizumab, interferon-alpha, और sorafenib have improved the आउटलुक for rcc.

the peritoneum ( ) is the serous झिल्ली कि फ़ॉर्म the lining of the abdominal cavity or the coelom —it कवर most of the intra-abdominal ( or coelomic ) organs—in amniotes and कुछ invertebrates ( annelids, लिये उदाहरण ).
it is composed of a layer of mesothelium समर्थित by a thin परत of संयोजी ऊतक.
The peritoneum दोनो supports the abdominal अंगों और serves as a conduit लिये उनके blood और लसीका vessels और nerves.
the abdominal गुहा ( the स्पेस bounded by the vertebrae, abdominal मांसपेशियां, diaphragm और श्रोणि मंजिल ) should नहीं be confused साथ the intraperitoneal space ( स्तिथ भीतर the abdominal गुहा, but लपेटा in peritoneum ).
the structures भीतर the intraperitoneal स्पेस are पुकारा `` intraperitoneal '' ( e.g. the पेट ), the structures in the abdominal cavity कि हैं स्तिथ पीछे the intraperitoneal space are called `` retroperitoneal `` ( e.g. the kidneys ), और those structures नीचे the intraperitoneal स्पेस are पुकारा `` subperitoneal '' or `` infraperitoneal '' ( e.g. the bladder ).

A solid-state ड्राइव ( ssd ) ( भी known as a solid-state disk or इलेक्ट्रॉनिक डिस्क, हालांकि it contains no वास्तविक `` डिस्क '' of any दयालु ) is a data storage device using integrated सर्किट assemblies as memory to store आंकड़ा persistently.
ssd प्रौद्योगिकी उपयोग electronic interfaces संगत साथ परंपरागत ब्लाक input/output ( I/O ) मुश्किल डिस्क ड्राइव.
SSDs have no moving mechanical components, जिससे फर्क them from traditional electromechanical magnetic डिस्क ऐसे as मुश्किल डिस्क ड्राइव ( hdds ) or फ्लॉपी डिस्क, जिससे contain spinning disks और movable read/write heads.
compared साथ electromechanical disks, ssds are typically less susceptible to शारीरिक शॉक, much quieter, have lower अभिगम time, and less विलंबता.
However, while the दाम of ssds रै जारी to मनाही in 2012, ssds हैं स्टिल परिचय 7 to 8 times अधिक expensive प्रति unit of भंडार than hdds.
Many ssds उपयोग I/O interfaces विकसित लिये मुश्किल disk ड्राइव, thus permitting सरल बदलना in आम अनुप्रयोग.
, सबसे ssds use nand-based फ्लैश मेमोरी, जिससे retains आंकड़ा बगैर power.
For applications requiring तेज़ अभिगम, but नहीं necessarily आंकड़ा हठ बाद शक्ति घाटा, ssds may be constructed इससे random-access मेमोरी ( राम ).
ऐसे डिवाइस may employ separate शक्ति स्त्रोत, such as batteries, to maintain data after power घाटा.
Hybrid ड्राइव or ठोस state संकर ड्राइव ( sshd ) combine the features of ssds and hdds in the वही ईकाई, containing a विशाल मुश्किल डिस्क ड्राइव and an SSD संचय to improve प्रदर्शन of frequently पहुँचा data.
These devices may offer near-ssd प्रदर्शन लिये अनेक अनुप्रयोग.

Caviar, according to the खाना and कृषि संगठन, is a product बना इससे salt-cured fish-eggs of the Acipenseridae परिवार.
the roe can be `` fresh '' ( non-pasteurized ) or pasteurized, साथ pasteurization reducing its culinary और economic मान.
traditionally the term caviar refers तभी to roe इससे जंगली sturgeon in the Caspian और ब्लैक समंदर ( Beluga, Ossetra and Sevruga caviars ).
Depending on the देश, caviar may भी be प्रयुक्त to describe the roe of अन्य मछली ऐसे as salmon, steelhead, ट्राउट, lumpfish, whitefish, और other प्रजाति of sturgeon.
caviar is माना a लक्ज़री कोमलता और is खाया as a garnish or a स्प्रेड.
