The 1990s, सुनाया और also ज्ञात as `` the Nineteen-Nineties '' or abbreviated as `` the nineties '' or `` the '90s '', was a decade that began on January 1, 1990, और ended on December 31, 1999.
it थी the 10th और पिछला decade of the 20th सदी और the 100th और पिछला दशक of the 2nd मिलेनियम.
the दशक is बेहतरीन ज्ञात for the end of the ठंडा युद्ध at the beginning of the दशक और the विस्तार और व्यावसायीकरण of the Internet दौरान the दूसरी हाफ of the दशक.
In much of the वेस्ट the 1990s is remembered as a काल of unprecedented peace और समृद्धि, हालांकि many भाग of the so-called तीसरा World faced विभिन्न problems सहित नरसंहार, AIDS और नई or continuing ethnic तनाव and सिविल wars.
culturally speaking the decade was characterized by the rise of multiculturalism और वैकल्पिक media.
आंदोलनों ऐसे as grunge, the rave झाँकी और hip हॉप स्प्रेड around the संसार to young लोगों during the decade, aided by then-new technology ऐसे as cable टेलीविज़न और the Internet.
a combination of कारकों, including the mass mobilization of capital बाज़ार through neoliberalism, the beginning of the फैली अप्रसार of नई मीडिया ऐसे as the अंतरजाल, और the विच्छेद of the Soviet Union led to a realignment and reconsolidation of आर्थिक और राजनैतिक power across the world, and within countries.
आय असमानता among countries in the संसार rose sharply between the 1980s और the mid-1990s, before levelling off और तब गिरना बाद 2000.

The संयुक्त States began इसके current सैन्य occupation of the मध्य East दौरान the summer of 1990 with Desert Shield बाद it cut off a विशाल portion of the संसार 's पेट्रोलियम सप्लाई.

The gray भेड़िया or grey भेड़िया ( Canis lupus ) is a species of canid देशी to the wilderness और रिमोट क्षेत्रों of North अमेरिका, Eurasia, and North Africa.
It is the largest member of इसके परिवार, with males averaging, और females.
it is similar in सामान्य रूप और proportions to a जर्मनी गड़रिये, or sled श्वान, लकिन रै a larger सिर, narrower chest, longer टाँगे, straighter टेल और बडे paws.
Its शीत फर is long और bushy, और predominantly a mottled gray in colour, हालांकि nearly pure श्वेत, रेड, or भूरा to ब्लैक also occur.
Within the genus canis, the gray wolf represents a more specialised and प्रगतिशील form than इसके छोटी cousins ( the coyote और golden jackal ), as demonstrated by its morphological adaptations to hunting विशाल शिकार, its अधिक मिलनसार प्रकृति और इसके अत्यधिक उन्नत expressive behavior.
it is a सोशल animal, travelling in nuclear परिवारों consisting of a mated pair, accompanied by the जोड़ी 's वयस्क औलाद.
The gray भेड़िया is typically an apex predator throughout इसके range, साथ only humans and टाइगर्स पोज़ a serious threat to it.
it फ़ीड्स primarily on विशाल ungulates, हालांकि it also eats छोटी पशु, livestock, carrion, और कचरा.
The धूसर भेड़िया is एक of the world 's most well researched animals, साथ probably more किताबे written about it than any अन्य वन्यजीव प्रजाति.
it रै a long इतिहास of association with humans, having महरूम despised और hunted in most agricultural समुदायों due to इसके हमले on पशुधन, while conversely होने आदरणीय by कुछ Native American जनजातियों.
It is the sole ancestor of the श्वान, जिससे थी पहला domesticated in the मध्य East.
Although the भय of wolves is प्रचलित in many इंसान समाजों, the majority of recorded attacks on people have been attributed to पशु suffering from rabies.
Non-rabid भेड़ियों have attacked and killed लोगों, mainly children, but this is असामान्य, as wolves हैं अपेक्षाकृत few, सजीव दूर इससे लोगों, और have been सिखाया to fear इंसानो by hunters और गड़रिये.
शिकार और trapping has घटाया the प्रजाति ' दायरा to, हालांकि इसके स्टिल अपेक्षाकृत फैली दायरा और stable जनसांख्यिकी अर्थात् कि the प्रजाति is not threatened at a वैश्विक स्तर, and is इसलिए वर्गीकृत by the आईयूसीएन as तनिक चिंता.
The Roman साम्राज्य ( ) थी the post- Republican काल of the प्राचीन Roman civilization, characterised by an autocratic रूप of सरकारी और large territorial holdings around the भूमध्यसागरीय in यूरोपीय, Africa, और Asia.
the 500-year-old Roman Republic, जिससे preceded it, था been destabilized through a श्रेणी of civil युद्धों.
Several कार्यक्रम marked the transition from गणतंत्र to Empire, including जूलियस Caesar 's appointment as perpetual तानाशाह ( 44 BC ) ; the Battle of actium ( 31 BC ) ; और the granting of the honorific augustus to octavian by the Roman सीनेट ( 27 bc ).
the first दो centuries of the साम्राज्य यहूद a काल of unprecedented स्थिरता और समृद्धि known as the pax romana ( `` Roman सलाम '' ).
it reached इसके महानतम expanse during the शासनकाल of त्राजान ( 98–117 ad ).
in the 3rd सदी, the साम्राज्य underwent a संकट that threatened its अस्तित्व, but थी reunified and stabilized अंतर्गत the emperors Aurelian और diocletian.
ईसाइयों रोज़ to शक्ति in the 4th सदी, during which समय a system of dual नियम थी developed in the लैटिन West और Greek East.
बाद the collapse of सेंट्रल सरकारी in the West in the 5th सदी, the eastern half जारी as कया would later be known as the Byzantine साम्राज्य.
क्युकी of the साम्राज्य 's विशाल extent और long endurance, the institutions and संस्कृति of रोम था a profound और lasting influence on the विकास of language, religion, architecture, philosophy, विधि, और फ़ॉर्म of government in the territory it governed, विशेषकर Europe, and by means of European expansionism throughout the modern world.
Education in the संयुक्त States is mainly provided by the पब्लिक sector, with control and funding coming इससे three levels : लोकल, राज्य, और संघीय, in that order.
Child शिक्षा is compulsory, and there हैं also a विशाल क्रमांक और चौड़ी किस्में of higher शिक्षा संस्थानों throughout the देश कि one can चुनें to attend, दोनो सरेआम और privately administered.
पब्लिक शिक्षा is universally उपलब्धियाँ.
स्कूल curricula, funding, शिक्षण, नियुक्ति, and अन्य policies are set through locally निर्वाचित स्कूल फलक साथ jurisdiction over school districts साथ many directives from राज्य legislatures.
स्कूल जिले are usually separate इससे अन्य लोकल jurisdictions, साथ independent officials और budgets.
Educational standards and standardized परीक्षण निर्णय are प्रायः made by state सरकारें.
The ages लिये अनिवार्य education vary by राज्य.
it begins from ages पाँच to eight and ends from आयु चौदह to अठारह.
अनिवार्य शिक्षा requirements can generally be संतुष्ट by educating children in पब्लिक स्कूलों, state-certified private स्कूलों, or an स्वीकृत घर स्कूल कार्यक्रम.
in सबसे public और निजी स्कूलों, education is divided into तीन levels : elementary school, middle स्कूल ( sometimes पुकारा जूनियर ऊँची school ), और high school ( sometimes referred to as द्वितीयक शिक्षा ).
In almost सब स्कूलों at ये स्तर, children are विभाजित by आयु groups into ग्रेड, ranging इससे किंडरगार्टन ( followed by पहला ग्रेड ) लिये the youngest children in elementary school, up to बारहवीं ग्रेड, the final year of ऊँची स्कूल.
the सटीक आयु range of विद्यार्थी in ये ग्रेड स्तर varies थोड़ा from क्षेत्रफल to क्षेत्रफल.
post-secondary शिक्षा, better known as `` कॉलेज `` in the United States, is generally governed separately इससे the elementary and ऊँची school प्रणाली, and is described in a separate section नीचे.
Government समर्थित, free पब्लिक स्कूलों for सब प्रारंभ being स्थापित after the क्रान्ति, और विस्तारित in the 19th सदी, as the results of efforts of men जैसे होरेस मन and बुकर T. वॉशिंगटन.
By 1870, सब राज्य था फ़्री elementary स्कूलों, albeit only in शहरी centers.
As the 20th सदी खींचा nearer, राज्य प्रारंभ passing laws to मेक schooling compulsory, और by 1910, 72 प्रतिशत of children attended स्कूल.
निजी स्कूलों जारी to स्प्रेड during this समय, as खूब as कॉलेजों and—in the ग्रामीण centers— जमीन grant कॉलेजों.
The साल of 1910 भी देखी the पहला सच्चा high schools.
दौरान the बाकी of the 20th सदी, educational प्रयत्न centered on reducing the inequality of the schooling प्रणाली.
The लैंडमार्क परम् अदालत case भूरा v. फलक of शिक्षा made the desegregation of elementary and ऊँची schools a नेशनल priority, जबकि the pell Grant कार्यक्रम helped poor अल्पसंख्यकों gain access to कॉलेज.
Special education was बना into federal law in 1975.
the Elementary and द्वितीयक शिक्षा अधिनियम of 1965 बना standardized परीक्षण a आवश्यकता, और in 1983, a commission was स्थापित to evaluate उनके परिणाम and propose a course of action.
the resulting no Child बाएँ Behind Act of 2001 थी controversial और इसके goals proved to be unrealistic.
A आयोग established in 2006 evaluated higher शिक्षा, but इसके सुझाव have yet to be fully implemented.
पॉल Bragg ( February 6, 1895 – December 7, 1976 ), nutritionist, was a pioneer in America’s तंदुरुस्ती movement.
स्वास्थ्य spending per capita, in $ us ppp-adjusted, with the US and कनाडा compared amongst अन्य पहला world nations.
तुलना of the स्वास्थ्य परवाह systems in Canada और the United States हैं often बना by सरकारी, public health और पब्लिक नीति analysts.
the two countries था similar स्वास्थ्य care systems पहले Canada reformed इसके प्रणाली in the 1960s और 1970s.
the संयुक्त राज्य spends much अधिक धन on health care than कनाडा, on both a per-capita आधार and as a प्रतिशत of GDP.
In 2006, per-capita बिता लिये स्वास्थ्य परवाह in कनाडा was us $ 3,678 ; in the u.S., us $ 6,714.
the U.S. खर्च 15.3 % of जीडीपी on health care in कि year ; कनाडा spent 10.0 %.
in 2006, 70 % of health care बिता in Canada was financed by government, बनाम 46 % in the संयुक्त राज्य.
कुल सरकारी spending per capita in the u.S. on health care was 23 % higher than कनाडाई सरकारी बिता, और u.S. government व्यय on स्वास्थ्य परवाह थी बस under 83 % of कुल कनाडाई spending ( पब्लिक और private ) though ये आंकडे do n't take into खाता population differences.
Studies have come to अलग conclusions about the परिणाम of इस disparity in बिता.
a 2007 पुनर्विलोकन of all अध्ययन comparing स्वास्थ्य outcomes in Canada and the us in a कनाडाई peer-reviewed चिकित्सा जर्नल मिला कि `` health outcomes may be श्रेष्ठ in मरीजों cared लिये in कनाडा versus the United States, लकिन मतभेद हैं नहीं सतत. ''
जीवन expectancy is longer in Canada, और इसके शिशु mortality रेट is निम्नतर than कि of the U.S., लकिन there is debate about the underlying causes of these differences.
One commonly cited तुलना, the 2000 World Health संगठन 's ratings of `` overall स्वास्थ्य सेवा performance '', which used a `` कम्पोजिट माप of उपलब्धि in the level of health, the distribution of स्वास्थ्य, the level of responsiveness और fairness of वित्तीय योगदान '', क्रमित कनाडा 30th and the US 37th among 191 member राष्ट्र.
इस पढ़ाई रेटेड the us `` responsiveness '', or विशेषता of सेवा for individuals receiving treatment, as 1st, compared साथ 7th लिये कनाडा.
While the average life expectancy for canadians थी 80.34 सालो compared साथ 78.6 सालो for निवासियों of the us, simply comparing the जीवन प्रत्याशा of दो groups साथ अलग racial makeup और अलग मोटापा rates is likely नहीं an effective way of determining which healthcare system is superior.
The जो 's पढ़ाई methods were criticized by कुछ analyses.
Although वहीँ is a माप of सर्वसम्मति that life-expectancy और infant मृत्यु चिह्नित the सबसे विश्वसनीय तरीके to compare nation-wide health परवाह, assuming the population makeup is similar, a हाल report by the congressional Research सेवा carefully summarizes कुछ हाल आंकड़ा and टीप the `` difficult research मुद्दे '' facing international comparisons.
the ध्वनि सोर्स रै अभी broken through the sound गति अवरोध, और is traveling at 1.4 times the speed of ध्वनि, ( mach 1.4 ).
Since the source is moving तेज़ ( with a गति ) than the sound लहरें it creates, it actually लीड the advancing तरंगाग्र.
the ध्वनि सोर्स होगा pass by a stationary observer ( साथ a गति ) before the observer दरअसल hears the ध्वनि it creates.
as a result, an निरीक्षक in front of the source होगा detect
and an observer पीछे the सोर्स.
A sonic boom produced by an aircraft चलती at M=2.92, गणना from the कोन कोण of 20 degrees.
an observer hears the boom when the शॉक वेव, on the edges of the कोन, crosses उसके or her स्थान.
mach कोन कोण
A सोनिक बूम is the sound associated साथ the shock लहरें created by an ऑब्जेक्ट traveling through the air faster than the गति of sound.
Sonic booms generate enormous amounts of ध्वनि energy, sounding much जैसे an विस्फोट.
the crack of a supersonic गोली passing overhead is an उदाहरण of a sonic boom in miniature.
the Tonight दिखाएँ with jay लीनो is an अमरीकी late-night बात show hosted by Jay लीनो कि initially aired from May 25, 1992 to may 29, 2009, and resumed production on March 1, 2010.

rfid चिप अगला to a अनाज of rice.
This चिप contains a radio-frequency electromagnetic field coil कि modulates an बाह्य magnetic फ़ील्ड to ट्रांसफ़र a coded identification क्रमांक when queried by a reader device.
This छोटी type is incorporated in consumer products, और implanted in पालतु, लिये पहचान उद्देश्य.
radio-frequency पहचान ( rfid ) is the बेतार non-contact use of radio-frequency इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक फ़ील्ड to transfer data, लिये the purposes of automatically identifying and tracking टैग attached to वस्तुएँ.
the टैग contain electronically भंडारित information.
Some टैग हैं powered और पढ़ा at छोटी सीमाएँ ( a few मीटर ) via चुम्बकीय फ़ील्ड ( इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक प्रेरण ).
अन्य use a local power source ऐसे as a बैटरी, or else have no battery but collect उर्जा इससे the interrogating EM फ़ील्ड, and then अधिनियम as a passive transponder to emit microwaves or uhf radio लहरें ( i.e., इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक विकिरण at ऊँची बारंबारता ).
Battery powered tags may operate at hundreds of meters.
नापसंद a बार कोड, the टैग does नहीं necessarily need to be within लकीर of sight of the रीडर, और may be embedded in the tracked object.
RFID टैग हैं used in many उद्योग.
an RFID tag संलग्न to an automobile दौरान उत्पादन can be प्रयुक्त to track इसके progress through the assembly line.
Pharmaceuticals can be tracked through warehouses.
पशुधन और pets may have टैग injected, allowing positive पहचान of the animal.
Since rfid टैग can be संलग्न to कपडे, possessions, or भी implanted भीतर लोगों, the सम्भावना of पढना personally-linked सूचना बगैर consent रै raised privacy चिंताएं.
Id, ego and super-ego हैं the तीन parts of the मानसिक apparatus defined in सिग्मुंड फ्रायड 's संरचनात्मक model of the psyche ; वे हैं the तीन सैद्धांतिक constructs in शर्तें of whose कार्यकलाप and बातचीत दिमागी जीवन is described.
According to इस मॉडल of the psyche, the id is the set of uncoordinated instinctual trends ; the super-ego plays the critical और moralizing role ; और the ego is the व्यवस्थित, realistic part that mediates between the इच्छाओं of the id and the super-ego.
the super-ego can stop you इससे doing certain बाते कि your id may want तुम to do.
Even हालांकि the model is संरचनात्मक और makes सन्दर्भ to an apparatus, the id, अहंकार and super-ego हैं कृत्यों of the mind rather than भाग of the brain और do नहीं correspond one-to-one साथ actual दैहिक structures of the दयालु dealt साथ by neuroscience.
the concepts themselves arose at a लेट स्टेज in the विकास of फ्रायड 's विचार : the `` structural मॉडल '' ( which succeeded उसके `` आर्थिक मॉडल '' and `` topographical मॉडल '' ) थी पहला discussed in his 1920 निबन्ध `` Beyond the Pleasure principle `` और थी formalized और elaborated upon तीन years बाद in उसके `` the अहंकार and the id ``.
फ्रायड 's प्रस्ताव was बहकावे by the ambiguity of the term `` unconscious `` and इसके अनेक conflicting uses.

the एयर फ़ोर्स आरक्षित Officer Training corps ( afrotc ) is एक of the तीन प्राथमिक commissioning स्त्रोत for officers in the United राज्य Air फ़ोर्स, the अन्य दो being the United राज्य एयर Force Academy ( USAFA ) और एयर फ़ोर्स अधिकारी Training स्कूल ( ots ).
a अधीनस्थ कमांड of the Air विश्वविद्यालयों भीतर the एयर Education और प्रशिक्षण कमांड ( aetc ), afrotc is aligned under the Jeanne M. Holm बीच for Officer Accessions और Citizen विकास at Maxwell afb, अलबामा.
the holm Center, formerly known as the एयर Force अधिकारी accession and प्रशिक्षण Schools ( afoats ), retains सीधा responsibility लिये both afrotc और OTS.
AFROTC is the largest और oldest सोर्स of commissioned अधिकारियों for the U.S. एयर फ़ोर्स.
AFROTC 's stated मिशन is to उपज विशेषता leaders लिये the u.S. एयर फ़ोर्स.
afrotc units हैं स्तिथ on 144 college and विश्वविद्यालयों campuses साथ 984 अतिरिक्त institutions of higher learning participating in cross-town समझौतों कि allow उनके विद्यार्थी to attend afrotc वर्ग at a आसपास `` मेजबान '' college or विश्वविद्यालयों.
According to afoats hq, in 2006, AFROTC commissioned 2,083 USAF Second Lieutenants, साथ afrotc नामांकन ranging इससे 23,605 in 1985 to 10,231 in 1993, और around 13,000 enrolled आज.
afrotc इकाई at colleges और विश्वविद्यालयों हैं पुकारा `` detachments, '' और are typically headed by an क्रियाशील ड्यूटी यूएसएएफ अधिकारी in the rank of कर्नल or lieutenant colonel who functions as both the detachment Commander लिये USAF उद्देश्य और साथ the nominal title of Professor of Aerospace अध्ययन ( pas ) भीतर the संस्था 's academic जातियाँ.
सबसे कॉलेजों और universities होगा designate the AFROTC detachment as the Department of Aerospace अध्ययन.
The pas is assisted by तीन to चार Assistant Professors of aerospace अध्ययन ( APAS ), सब active ड्यूटी यूएसएएफ officers in the बाँधने of प्रमुख or captain.
तीन USAF non-commissioned अधिकारियों and एक वरिष्ठ non-commissioned अधिकारी होगा typically provide सैन्य प्रशासनिक support और are often augmented by one to two civilian स्टाफ support employees of the academic संस्था.
भीतर AFROTC detachments, the विद्यार्थी ( referred to as `` cadets '' ) are व्यवस्थित into विंग्स, groups, squadrons, और flights, mirroring the यूएसएएफ कार्यात्मक wing ढांचा.
the AFROTC detachment 's cadet wing or cadet समूह is separated into दो विभाजन : the सामान्य Military Course ( GMC ) consisting of the पहला दो सालो of प्रशिक्षण, और the Professional अधिकारी Course ( poc ) consisting of the पिछला two सालो of प्रशिक्षण.
the AFROTC कार्यक्रम is also divided into two training कृत्यों : the Academic Classroom कार्यक्रम ( aerospace अध्ययन classes ) और cadet Activities ( i.e., नेतृत्व प्रयोगशाला, शारीरिक Training, and अन्य training ).
पेपर density ( भी known as आधार वज़न और grammage ) is a term प्रयुक्त in the pulp and पेपर उद्योग and भी लिये कपड़ा उद्योग to denote a measure of mass of the product प्रति unit of क्षेत्रफल लिये a प्रकार of fabric, पेपर or paperboard.
The पद `` घनत्व '' is not used in इसके traditional sense of द्रव्यमान प्रति ईकाई आवाज़.
`` Paper density '', बल्कि, is a measure of the क्षेत्रफल घनत्व.
Paper उत्पाद कि let छोटी or no लाइट pass through ( e.g. poster फलक ) are माना dense or heavy.
Paper उत्पाद कि allow some लाइट to pass through ( e.g. ऊतक paper ) are माना lightweight.
in the pulp और पेपर उद्योग, it is आम to set a commercial पेपर machine to उपज पेपर to a निशाना पेपर घनत्व.
Paper density can also be used to distinguish पेपर from paperboard as the latter प्रायः has a grammage वृहद than 134 g/m2.
Two तरीके of expressing paper घनत्व are commonly उपयोगd:
Expressed in गामा प्रति वर्गाकार मीटर ( g/m2 ), पेपर density is भी ज्ञात as grammage.
इस is the माप used in सबसे भाग of the संसार.
expressed in terms of the mass ( expressed as weight ) per क्रमांक of चादरें, it is known as आधार वज़न.
the सम्मेलन used in the संयुक्त राज्य और a few अन्य देशों using us paper आकार is पाउंड of a ream of 500 ( or in कुछ cases 1000 ) चादरें of a दिए ( कच्चा, स्टिल uncut ) basis size.
Japanese पेपर is expressed as the वज़न in kg of 1000 sheets.

a खाना मार्गदर्शिका पिरामिड is a पिरामिड shaped मार्गदर्शिका of स्वस्थ भोजन विभाजित into भाग to दिखाएँ the अनुशंसित सेवन लिये प्रत्येक खाना group.
the पहला खाना पिरामिड थी published in स्वीडन in 1974.
The सबसे widely ज्ञात food पिरामिड थी introduced by the United States Department of कृषि in the साल 1992, थी updated in 2005, और तब replaced in 2011.

Hans ईसाई andersen ( ; प्रायः referred to in scandinavia as H. C. andersen ; April 2, 1805august 4, 1875 ) थी a डैनिश author and कवि.
हालांकि a prolific writer of plays, travelogues, novels, और poems, andersen is बेहतरीन remembered for उसके परी tales, a साहित्यिक genre he so mastered that he खुद रै become as mythical as the किस्से he लिखा.
Andersen 's लोकप्रियता is not सीमित to children ; his stories—called, or `` fantastic किस्से '' —express themes कि transcend आयु and राष्ट्रीयता.
दौरान उसके आजीवन he was acclaimed for having delighted children worldwide and was feted by royalty.

नजर सम्पर्क occurs जब `` two people dekh at प्रत्येक अन्य 's आँखें at the same समय. ''
in human beings, eye सम्पर्क is a रूप of nonverbal संचार and is विचार to have a विशाल influence on सोशल behavior.
Coined in the जल्दी to mid-1960s, the term रै आइये in the वेस्ट to प्रायः define the अधिनियम as a meaningful और important sign of confidence और सोशल संचार.
the कस्टम और significance of नजर सम्पर्क vary widely between cultures, साथ धार्मिक और सोशल मतभेद प्रायः altering इसके अर्थ greatly.
the study of नजर contact is sometimes ज्ञात as oculesics.
bed bugs are parasitic कीट of the cimicid family कि feed exclusively on blood.
the term most commonly refers to members of the genus cimex of जिससे cimex lectularius, the common bed कीड़ा, is the बेहतरीन ज्ञात as it prefers to फीड on इंसान रक्त हालांकि अन्य cimex species are specialized to other animals, e.g., bat bugs, C. pipistrelli ( यूरोपीय ), C. pilosellus ( western US ), और C. adjunctus ( entire पूर्वी US ).
the name of the `` bed कीड़ा '' is निकला from the preferred आवास of cimex lectularius : गरम घरों और especially आसपास or अंदर of beds और bedding or other sleep क्षेत्रों.
bed बग हैं मुख्यतः active at रात्रि, but हैं नहीं exclusively nocturnal.
They usually फीड on their होस्ट without होने noticed.
a क्रमांक of प्रतिकूल स्वास्थ्य प्रभाव may परिणाम from bed bug bites, including स्किन rashes, मनोवैज्ञानिक effects, और allergic लक्षण.
निदान involves दोनो ढूंढना bed bugs and the occurrence of संगत लक्षण.
Bed बग have महरूम ज्ञात as इंसान परजीवी लिये हज़ारों of सालो.
at a पाइंट in the early 1940s, they were mostly eradicated in the विकसित संसार, लकिन have increased in prevalence since 1995.
क्युकी infestation of human habitats रै महरूम on the बढ़ाएँ, bed कीड़ा bites और related conditions have महरूम on the वृद्धि as well.
The किताब of Isaiah ( ) is the पहला of the latter Prophets in the यहूदी बाइबल, preceding ezekiel, यिर्मयाह और the किताब of the Twelve.
( the अनुक्रम of the subsequent किताबे differs somewhat in the Christian Old वसीयत ).
The first 39 chapters prophesy यातना लिये a sinful Judah और for सब the nations of the संसार कि oppose परमेश्वर, जबकि the पिछला 27 prophesy the restoration of the स्वदेश of इसराईल और a नई सृष्टि in God 's glorious future किंगडम ; this section शामिल the गीतों of the कष्ट नौकर, four separate passages referring to the nation of इसराईल, interpreted by ईसाइयों as prefiguring the coming of यीशु मसीह.
Tradition ascribes authorship of the किताब to यशायाह son of Amoz, but अभी विद्वानों widely सहमत that the book is the कार्य of तीन अलग लेखक - few scholars इनकार इस view, और those कि do, do so for theological reasons.
the पहला, termed proto-isaiah ( अध्याय 1–39 ), contains the शब्द of the 8th-century bce नबी साथ 7th-century bce expansions ; the दूसरी, deutero-isaiah ( अध्याय 40–55 ), is the कार्य of a 6th-century bce author writing निकट the end of the Babylonian captivity ; and the तीसरा, the काव्य trito-isaiah ( chapters 56–66 ), was रचित in Jerusalem shortly बाद the वापसी इससे निर्वासन, probably by अनेक authors.
ऑरेगॉन State विश्वविद्यालयों ( osu ) is a coeducational, पब्लिक शोध विश्वविद्यालयों स्तिथ in Corvallis, Oregon, संयुक्त States.
The विश्वविद्यालयों offers undergraduate, graduate और डॉक्टरेट degrees और a multitude of शोध opportunities.
वहीँ are more than 200 academic degree कार्यक्रम offered through the university.
osu 's programs in microbiology, नाभिकीय अभियान्त्रिकी, पारिस्थितिकी, forestry, पब्लिक health, biochemistry, zoology, oceanography, food science और pharmacy हैं recognized nationally as शीर्ष टियर कार्यक्रम.
the OSU 's liberal कला कार्यक्रम have भी grown significantly and the विभाग is माना a `` cornerstone '' of the institution.
More than 200,000 people have attended OSU since इसके founding.
The Carnegie न्यास classifies Oregon राज्य विश्वविद्यालयों as part of इसके शीर्ष टियर of शोध संस्थानों.
as of 2008, osu is one of only seventy-three land-grant विश्वविद्यालयों.
the स्कूल is भी recognized as a sea-grant, space-grant और sun-grant संस्था, making it एक of only two us संस्थानों to retain all चार designations and the तभी पब्लिक विश्वविद्यालयों to do so ( कॉर्नेल is the only अन्य साथ समान designations ).
as एक of the two फ्लैगशिप universities of the Oregon विश्वविद्यालयों System, osu receives more funding for शोध, annually, than सब other पब्लिक उच्चतर education संस्थानों in ऑरेगॉन combined.
मादा ejaculation is the expulsion of fluid by human महिलाओं from the paraurethral नलिकाएं through and around the मादा urethra during or पहले an orgasm.
it is भी ज्ञात colloquially as gushing or squirting, although these are considered to be अलग phenomena in some शोध publications.

the kanab ambersnail, scientific name Oxyloma haydeni kanabensis or Oxyloma kanabense, is a critically endangered subspecies or प्रजाति of small, air-breathing land snail, a स्थलीय pulmonate gastropod mollusc in the परिवार Succineidae, the amber घोंघे.
The आम नाम of the एम्बर घोंघे is based on the shell, which is पारदर्शी और जब खाली प्रायः resembles एम्बर in रंग.
This प्रजाति is endemic to the संयुक्त राज्य, specifically the राज्य of Arizona और Utah, जहाँ it थी पहला एकत्रित in the early 20th सदी.
it has महरूम सूचीबद्ध as endangered on the United राज्य मछली और Wildlife Service सूची of endangered species since 8 August 1991.
इस घोंघा जीवनदान in wetlands, स्रोतों, and seeps, और तभी two of इसके natural habitats are known to exist : Three Lakes, a meadow near kanab, यूटा, and Vasey 's स्वर्ग, a वसन्त साथ the कोलोराडो River भीतर Grand canyon नेशनल पार्क.
in इसके natural habitat it is बल्कि polyphagous, feeding मुख्यतः on bacteria, plants and fungi, और reproduces during the गर्मियाँ.
अभी considered a critically endangered प्रजाति on the आईयूसीएन रेड सूची of Threatened Species due to a श्रेणी of कारकों ( सहित influence ), the Kanab ambersnail has been reintroduced to three स्रोतों ऊपर the ऐतिहासिक ऊँची जल स्तर साथ the कोलोराडो River.
The स्पेनी language is the दूसरी सबसे used भाषा in the United States.
There are अधिक स्पेनी speakers in the संयुक्त राज्य than there हैं speakers of Chinese, फ्रेंच, जर्मनी, Italian, हवाई, and the Native American भाषाएं combined.
According to the 2010 अमरीकी जातियाँ सर्वेक्षण conducted by the u.S. Census ब्यूरो, Spanish is the primary language spoken at घर by almost 37 million people aged पाँच or पुरानी, a फिगर more than दोगुना that of 1990.

Roughly हाफ of all U.S. स्पेनी अध्यक्षों also speak अंग्रेज़ी `` बहुत well, '' आधारित on the self-assessment Census question respondents.

Sedimentary rocks are प्रकार of चट्टान कि हैं formed by the deposition of सामग्री at the धरती 's सतह and भीतर bodies of water.
sedimentation is the collective नाम लिये processes कि कारण mineral and/or सशुल्क particles ( detritus ) to settle और accumulate or खनिज to precipitate इससे a समाधान.
अणु that रूप a sedimentary चट्टान by accumulating are called sediment.
पहले being deposited, sediment थी formed by weathering and erosion in a source area, और तब transported to the प्लेस of deposition by water, wind, बर्फ, द्रव्यमान गति or glaciers which are called agents of denudation.
the sedimentary rock cover of the महाद्वीपों of the धरती 's क्रस्ट is extensive, but the total contribution of sedimentary rocks is अनुमानित to be तभी 8 % of the कुल volume of the क्रस्ट.
sedimentary rocks हैं तभी a thin veneer over a crust consisting mainly of igneous and metamorphic रॉक्स.
sedimentary रॉक्स हैं deposited in परतों as strata, forming a ढांचा पुकारा bedding.
the पढ़ाई of sedimentary rocks and rock strata provides सूचना परिचय the subsurface कि is उपयोगी लिये civil अभियान्त्रिकी, लिये उदाहरण in the निर्माण of सड़कें, घरों, tunnels, canals or अन्य constructions.
sedimentary rocks हैं भी महत्वपूर्ण sources of natural संसाधन जैसे कोयले, चट्टान fuels, पीने जल or ores.
The study of the अनुक्रम of sedimentary rock strata is the प्रमुख source लिये scientific ज्ञान परिचय the धरती 's history, including palaeogeography, paleoclimatology and the इतिहास of जीवन.
the scientific अनुशासन that studies the गुण और उत्पत्ति of sedimentary रॉक्स is पुकारा sedimentology.
sedimentology is दोनो भाग of geology and physical geography और overlaps partly with अन्य disciplines in the धरती sciences, ऐसे as pedology, geomorphology, भूरसायन or structural geology.

संत पैट्रिक ( ; ; Modern ; ; c. 387 – 17 कूच c. 460 or c. 492 ) थी a romano-british ईसाई missionary and bishop in आयरलैंड.
ज्ञात as the `` apostle of Ireland '', he is the primary patron संत of the द्वीप साथ साथ संतो Brigid और columba.
दो प्रामाणिक अक्षर इससे उसे जीवित, इससे which come the तभी generally accepted विवरण of उसके जीवन.
जब he was about 16, he थी captured इससे his home and लिया as a स्लेव to आयरलैंड, where he lived लिये six years before escaping और returning to उसके family.
बाद बनने a cleric, he लौटे to उत्तरी and western आयरलैंड as an ordained bishop, but little is ज्ञात परिचय the places जहाँ he worked.
by the seventh सदी, he था already come to be revered as the संरक्षक संत of Ireland.
Most available विवरण of उसके जीवन are from subsequent hagiographies, and these हैं अभी not स्वीकृत without विस्तृत आलोचना.
the annals of ulster state that he arrived in Ireland in 432, ministered in Ulster around 443, and died in 457 or 461.
The टेक्स्ट, however, distinguishes between `` बूढ़ा पैट्रिक '' ( विचार to mean palladius ) और `` पैट्रिक, archapostle of the स्कॉट्स, '' जो died in 492.
the वास्तविक तिथियाँ of पैट्रिक 's जीवन can नहीं be फिक्स्ड साथ certainty but, on a widespread interpretation, he थी active as a मिशनरी in Ireland दौरान the दूसरी half of the 5th सदी.
he is generally credited साथ होने the पहला bishop of Armagh, Primate of All आयरलैंड.
संत पैट्रिक 's दिन is observed on March 17, the तिथि of उसके death.
it is मनाये दोनो inside और outside आयरलैंड, as दोनो a religious और, विशेषकर बाहर Ireland, धर्मनिरपेक्ष अवकाश.
In the dioceses of आयरलैंड, it is दोनो a solemnity and a holy day of दायित्व ; बाहर आयरलैंड, it can be a जश्न of Ireland itself.
लकीर segments in the golden अनुपात
A golden आयताकार साथ longer side a और shorter side b, when लगाई सटा to a वर्गाकार with sides of length a, होगा उपज a समान golden rectangle with longer पक्ष a + b and shorter side a.
This illustrates the संबंध.
In गणित and the कला, दो quantities हैं in the सुनहरी ratio if the ratio of the sum of the quantities to the larger quantity is equal to the ratio of the larger quantity to the छोटी one.
The figure on the सही illustrates the ज्यामितीय संबंध.

where the यूनानी letter फाई ( ) represents the golden ratio.

the golden अनुपात is भी called the golden खण्ड ( Latin : sectio ओरिया ) or golden औसत.
Other names include extreme and औसत अनुपात, medial section, दैवी proportion, divine खण्ड ( Latin : sectio divina ), सुनहरी proportion, सुनहरी cut, and सुनहरी क्रमांक.
अनेक 20th सदी artists और आर्किटेक्ट have proportioned उनके works to approximate the सुनहरी ratio—especially in the form of the golden rectangle, in which the अनुपात of the longer पक्ष to the shorter is the सुनहरी ratio—believing इस proportion to be aesthetically pleasing ( देखिए अनुप्रयोग और observations नीचे ).
mathematicians since यूक्लिड have पढ़ाई the गुण of the सुनहरी अनुपात, सहित इसके रूप in the आयाम of a regular प्रस्तुतीकरण और in a सुनहरी आयताकार, which can be cut into a वर्गाकार और a छोटी आयताकार with the same aspect अनुपात.
the सुनहरी ratio रै also महरूम प्रयुक्त to analyze the proportions of प्राकृतिक वस्तुएँ as खूब as man-made प्रणालियों ऐसे as financial markets, in कुछ cases based on dubious fits to आंकड़ा.
North myrtle बीच is a तटीय रिज़ॉर्ट city in horry काउंटी, दक्षिण Carolina, United राज्य.
It थी निर्मित in 1968 इससे four मौजूदा municipalities उत्तर of Myrtle Beach, और serves as one of the प्राथमिक tourist towns साथ the ग्रैंड strand.
the population was 13,752 at the 2010 census.
World युद्ध i ( WWI ) was a वैश्विक युद्ध केंद्रित in Europe that began on 28 जुलाई 1914 और lasted जबतक 11 नवम्बर 1918.
It थी predominantly पुकारा the संसार युद्ध or the ग्रेट युद्ध इससे its occurrence until the start of World War II in 1939, and the पहला World युद्ध or World युद्ध i thereafter.
It शामिल सब the world 's ग्रेट powers, जिससे were समवेत in दो opposing alliances : the allies ( based on the Triple Entente of the United Kingdom, फ़्रांस और Russia ) and the सेंट्रल शक्तियां ( originally the ट्रिपल Alliance of Germany, austria-hungary and इटली ; लकिन, as Austria–Hungary था taken the offensive विरूद्ध the agreement, इटली did not डालें into the war ).
These alliances यहूद दोनो reorganised और विस्तारित as अधिक राष्ट्र डाला the युद्ध : इटली, जापानी और the संयुक्त राज्य joined the Allies, and the उस्मानी साम्राज्य and Bulgaria the सेंट्रल शक्तियां.
ultimately, more than 70 लाख सैन्य कर्मियों, सहित 60 million europeans, यहूद mobilised in एक of the largest wars in history.
More than 9 million combatants were मारे, largely क्युकी of technological advancements कि led to enormous increases in the lethality of weapons without सम्बन्धित सुधार in सुरक्षा or mobility.
it was the fifth- deadliest विरोध in संसार इतिहास, subsequently paving the रास्ता for विभिन्न political परिवर्तन, such as revolutions in many of the राष्ट्र involved.
एक of the long-term causes of the युद्ध थी the resurgence of साम्राज्यवाद in the foreign नीतियों of the ग्रेट powers of यूरोपीय.
More तत्काल, the assassination of archduke फ्रांज फर्डिनेंड of Austria, the heir to the सिंहासन of austria-hungary, on 28 जून 1914 by Yugoslav राष्ट्रवादी Gavrilo princip in साराजेवो triggered a राजनयिक संकट जब Austria-Hungary subsequently वितरित an ultimatum to the Kingdom of सर्बिया.
अनेक alliances formed over the पिछला दशकों यहूद invoked.
भीतर weeks, the प्रमुख शक्तियां were at war and, via their colonies, the conflict जल्द स्प्रेड around the world.
On 28 जुलाई, the austro-hungarians fired the first गोलियाँ of the war as preparation लिये the आक्रमण of सर्बिया.
जबकि the russians mobilised, the Germans invaded neutral बेल्जियम and ध्वज on the way to France, providing a casus belli लिये ब्रिटेन 's घोषणा of युद्ध against जर्मनी.
बाद the German कूच on पेरिस थी brought to a halt—the so-called Miracle of the marne —the पश्चिमी सामने settled into a static बैटल of अपघर्षण साथ a गर्त line that changed little जबतक 1917.
On the Eastern Front, the रूसी army थी कामयाब विरूद्ध the Austro-Hungarians, but थी रोका in इसके आक्रमण of ईस्ट Prussia by the Germans.
In November the Ottoman साम्राज्य joined the war, खोलने up fronts in the काकेशस, मेसोपोटामिया और the sinai.
इटली और बुल्गारिया went to युद्ध in 1915 और Romania in 1916.
in रूस, the त्सार 's सरकारी collapsed in कूच 1917 और a subsequent क्रान्ति in November brought the russians to शर्तें साथ the सेंट्रल शक्तियां.
बाद a 1918 जर्मनी अप्रिय साथ the पश्चिमी front, the Allies drove back the germans in a series of successful offensives और American शक्तियां began entering the trenches.
जर्मनी, जिससे था इसके own ट्रबल साथ revolutionaries, सहमत to an armistice on 11 November 1918.
the युद्ध ended in victory लिये the Allies.
कार्यक्रम on the home fronts were as tumultuous as on the बैटल fronts, as the participants आजमाया to mobilize उनके manpower and economic संसाधन to fight a कुल war.
by the समाप्त of the war, चार major imperial powers—the जर्मनी, Russian, austro-hungarian and Ottoman empires—ceased to मौजूद.
the successor राज्य of the former two lost a ग्रेट amount of territory, while the latter two यहूद dismantled entirely.
the मैप of सेंट्रल Europe थी redrawn into अनेक smaller राज्य.
The लीग of राष्ट्र थी formed in the hope of preventing another such विरोध.
The European nationalism शाखित by the युद्ध और the ब्रेकअप of empires, the परखना of जर्मनी 's शिकस्त and problems साथ the Treaty of versailles are सहमत to be कारकों contributing to World War II.
Camden is a city in camden काउंटी, नई जर्सी, संयुक्त States.
It is the काउंटी सीट, स्तिथ across the डेलावेयर River इससे फिलाडेल्फिया.
As of the 2010 संयुक्त राज्य जनसांख्यिकी the नगर था a कुल जनसांख्यिकी of 77,344, representing a मनाही of 2,560 ( 3.2 % ) from the 79,904 residents enumerated दौरान the 2000 जनसांख्यिकी, which had in फेरे declined by 7,588 ( 8.7 % ) from the 87,492 गिने in the 1990 जनसांख्यिकी.
camden ranked as the 12th-most populous नगरपालिका in the राज्य in 2010 after having been क्रमित 10th in 2000.
Camden थी originally incorporated as a city on February 13, 1828, इससे portions of the now-defunct न्यूटन township, while the area थी स्टिल भाग of Gloucester काउंटी.
On March 13, 1844, Camden became भाग of the newly formed camden काउंटी.

A कंप्यूटर is a सामान्य purpose device कि can be programmed to carry out a finite set of arithmetic or लॉजिकल परिचालन.
Since a अनुक्रम of operations can be readily बदला, the computer can solve more than एक kind of प्रॉब्लम.

The पहला electronic digital कंप्यूटर were developed between 1940 और 1945 in the संयुक्त Kingdom और संयुक्त राज्य.

An inning, or innings, is a fixed-length खण्ड of a खेल in कोई of a किस्में of खेल – most notably क्रिकेट और baseball दौरान जिससे एक टोली कोशिशें to स्कोर while the अन्य team attempts to prevent the पहला इससे scoring.
in cricket, the पद innings is दोनो एकवचन और बहुवचन and is always spelled और pronounced साथ the टर्मिनल `` s ''.
In बेसबॉल और softball, the singular form is inning and तभी the plural takes an `` s ''.
In अनेक अन्य खेल, the लंबाई of the खेल is लिखवाई by a क्लॉक और टीमों स्वैप offensive और defensive भूमिकाएँ dynamically by लेने possession of a बॉल or समान item.
In बेसबॉल and क्रिकेट, however, एक team, कहा to be `` बल्लेबाजी '', कोशिशें to स्कोर `` रनों '' —see चलाएं ( बेसबॉल ) और run ( क्रिकेट ) —while the other team, कहा to be `` क्षेत्ररक्षण '', कोशिशें to prevent the स्कोरिंग of रनों और मिलेंगी सदस्यों of the बल्लेबाजी team आउट.
the टीमों switch स्थान after the fielding टोली has succeeded in getting a फिक्स्ड number of खिलाड़ी out, बनाना a क्लॉक अनावश्यक.
in cricket, the पद पारी is भी used to refer to the play of एक particular खिलाड़ी ( स्मिथ था a ग़रीब पारी, स्कोरिंग तभी 12 ).
by एक्सटेंशन, इस पद can be प्रयुक्त in अंग्रेजों अंग्रेज़ी लिये लगभग कोई कार्यकलाप which takes a काल of time ( the Liberal government था a शुभ पारी, but finally lost दफ्तर in 1972, or तुम 've had a मेला पारी, अभी it 's my turn, अर्थ `` you have बोला लिये long enough, now let me speak '' ).
it is भी प्रयुक्त in reference to someone जो has died at a reasonably बूढ़ा आयु or जिया a rich और rewarding जीवन ( ah, खूब.
John थी 89.
At least he था a शुभ innings ).

Adenosine deaminase deficiency, also पुकारा एडीए deficiency or ada-scid, is an autosomal recessive metabolic disorder कि कल्याणकारी immunodeficiency.
It occurs in fewer than one in 100,000 सजीव births worldwide.
it accounts लिये about 15 % of all cases of कठोर combined immunodeficiency ( SCID ).
it is very rare, you have a 3 % मौका of getting this gene.

Poverty is the राज्य of एक who lacks a निश्चित राशि of सामग्री possessions or धन.
निरपेक्ष poverty or destitution refers to the पिछडे of basic इंसान needs, which commonly शामिल food, water, स्वच्छता, कपडे, shelter, स्वास्थ्य परवाह और शिक्षा.
Relative गरीबी is defined contextually as economic inequality in the स्थान or society in which people live.
लिये much of इतिहास, गरीबी was माना largely अपरिहार्य as परंपरागत मोड्स of उत्पादन यहूद insufficient to दे an संपूर्ण population a comfortable मानक of जीना.
बाद the industrial revolution, द्रव्यमान उत्पादन in कारखानों बना माल increasingly more inexpensive और accessible.
of more importance is the modernization of agriculture, ऐसे as fertilizers, in अनुक्रम to provide enough उपज to फीड the जनसांख्यिकी.
the सप्लाई of मौलिक needs can be restricted by constraints on सरकारी services ऐसे as भ्रष्टाचार, tax avoidance, कर्ज़ और ऋण conditionalities and by the brain drain of स्वास्थ्य care और शैक्षणिक professionals.
रणनीति of increasing income to make मौलिक needs अधिक affordable typically शामिल welfare, आर्थिक freedoms, and providing financial services.
Poverty reduction is a प्रमुख लक्ष्य and समस्या for अनेक international संगठन ऐसे as the संयुक्त Nations and the संसार Bank.
The World Bank अनुमानित 1.29 billion लोगों यहूद living in absolute गरीबी in 2008.
Of ये, about 400 million people in निरपेक्ष गरीबी जिया in India और 173 लाख लोगों in चीन.
in USA 1 in 5 children lives in poverty.
in शर्तें of percentage of regional populations, sub-saharan अफ़्रीकी at 47 % था the highest incidence रेट of absolute गरीबी in 2008.
Between 1990 और 2010, about 663 million लोगों moved above the absolute गरीबी level.
स्टिल, extreme गरीबी is a वैश्विक challenge ; it is observed in all भाग of the संसार, सहित the विकसित economies.
मशरूम विषाक्तता ( also ज्ञात as mycetism ) refers to नुकसानदेह प्रभाव इससे ingestion of toxic substances उपस्थित in a mushroom.
These लक्षण can vary इससे पतला जठरांत्र तकलीफ to मौत.
the toxins उपस्थित are द्वितीयक metabolites उत्पादित in specific biochemical pathways in the fungal कोशिकाएं.
मशरूम poisoning is usually the result of ingestion of जंगली मशरूम बाद misidentification of a toxic mushroom as an edible species.
the सबसे आम कारण for इस misidentification is close प्रतिरूप in शर्तें of रंग और सामान्य morphology of the toxic mushrooms species साथ खाद्य प्रजाति.
Even बहुत अनुभवी जंगली mushroom gatherers are upon विरल अवसर poisoned by खाने toxic प्रजाति, despite होने खूब जागरूक of the risks, through carelessness.
to prevent mushroom poisoning, मशरूम gatherers need to be बहुत familiar साथ the mushrooms they intend to collect as खूब as साथ any similar-looking toxic प्रजाति.
In जोड, edibility of mushrooms may निर्भर on methods of तैयारी लिये कुकिंग.
Collectors भी need to be खूब aware कि edibility or toxicity of कुछ species varies with भौगोलिक स्थान.
इंसान ऊँचाई is the अलहदा from the bottom of the feet to the top of the head in a human देह, standing वीर्यपात.
When populations share genetic पृष्ठभूमि और environmental कारकों, average ऊँचाई is अक्सर characteristic within the समूह.
असाधारण ऊँचाई विभिन्नता ( around 20 % deviation इससे average ) within such a जनसांख्यिकी is sometimes due to gigantism or dwarfism, which हैं चिकित्सा शर्तें caused by विशिष्ट genes or अंतःस्रावी abnormalities.
In regions of extreme poverty or prolonged warfare, पर्यावरणीय कारकों like chronic malnutrition during childhood or किशोरावस्था may खाता for delayed growth and/or ( in severe मामले ) चिह्नित reductions in वयस्क stature भी बगैर the उपस्थिति of कोई of ये चिकित्सा शर्तें.
अपोलो 11 थी the spaceflight कि उतरा the first इंसानो, Americans Neil Armstrong और बज़ Aldrin, on the चंद्रमा on जुलाई 20, 1969, at 20:18 UTC.

Armstrong खर्च about दो और a half घंटों बाहर the spacecraft, एल्ड्रिन थोड़ा कम ; and साथ they collected of चंद्र material for वापसी to धरती.
a third member of the mission, Michael कॉलिन्स, piloted the कमांड spacecraft alone in चंद्र कक्षा until आर्मस्ट्रांग and एल्ड्रिन returned to it just अंतर्गत a day later लिये the trip वापस to धरती.
शुभारम्भ by a शनि v प्रक्षेपास्त्र इससे Kennedy Space Center in merritt द्वीप, फ्लोरिडा on जुलाई 16, Apollo 11 was the fifth manned mission of नासा 's अपोलो कार्यक्रम.
The अपोलो spacecraft था three parts : a कमांड मोड्यूल साथ a केबिन लिये the three astronauts जिससे थी the only part जिससे उतरा वापस on धरती ; a सेवा Module which समर्थित the कमांड मोड्यूल साथ नोदन, electrical शक्ति, oxygen और water ; and a चंद्र Module for landing on the चंद्रमा.
बाद होने भेजा to the चंद्रमा by the शनि v 's upper स्टेज, the astronauts अलग the spacecraft from it और travelled for three दिनों until वे entered into चंद्र orbit.
आर्मस्ट्रांग and एल्ड्रिन then moved into the चंद्र मोड्यूल और landed in the समुद्र of tranquility.
वे stayed a कुल of about 21 and a हाफ hours on the चंद्र सतह.
बाद उठाने off in the upper part of the Lunar मोड्यूल और rejoining कॉलिन्स in the कमांड मोड्यूल, वे returned to Earth और उतरा in the Pacific समंदर on July 24.
Broadcast on live TV to a world-wide audience, आर्मस्ट्रांग stepped onto the चंद्र surface and वर्णित the event as `` one छोटी step for [ a ] man, one giant छलांग for mankind. ''
Apollo 11 effectively ended the स्पेस रेस और fulfilled a नेशनल goal प्रस्तावित in 1961 by the लेट U.S. अध्यक्ष John F. कैनेडी in a speech पहले the United States Congress, `` before this दशक is out, of लैंडिंग a man on the चंद्रमा and returning him सकुशल to the धरती. ''
The फीफा संसार Cup, प्रायः बस the World कप, is an अंतरराष्ट्रीय association फ़ुटबॉल प्रतियोगिता लडे by the senior men 's नेशनल टीमों of the members of Fédération internationale de फ़ुटबॉल Association ( FIFA ), the खेल 's वैश्विक शासी देह.
the championship रै been awarded प्रत्येक चार years since the inaugural टूर्नामेंट in 1930, except in 1942 और 1946 when it थी नहीं आयोजित because of the Second संसार War.
the वर्तमान champions are स्पेन, जो जीती the 2010 टूर्नामेंट.
The वर्तमान format of the टूर्नामेंट involves 32 teams स्पर्धा लिये the title at venues within the मेजबान nation ( s ) over a period of about a माह ; इस phase is often पुकारा the संसार Cup फाइनल.
a qualification phase, जिससे फिलहाल takes place over the preceding तीन सालो, is प्रयुक्त to determine which टीमों qualify लिये the टूर्नामेंट साथ with the मेजबान स्वदेश ( s ).
the 19 संसार कप tournaments have महरूम जीती by eight अलग नेशनल टीमों.
ब्राज़ील have won five times, and वे हैं the only टोली to have निभाई in every tournament.
The other World कप winners हैं इटली, साथ four titles ; जर्मनी, with three शीर्षक ; अर्जेंटीना और inaugural winners उरुग्वे, with two शीर्षक प्रत्येक ; और इंग्लैण्ड, फ़्रांस, and स्पेन, with एक title प्रत्येक.
the World कप is the world 's सबसे widely viewed sporting event ; an अनुमानित 715.1 million लोगों देखी the फाइनल मैच of the 2006 फीफा संसार Cup held in जर्मनी.

नरसंहार is a पद coined in 1944 by राफेल lemkin to describe the deliberate और systematic विनाश, in पूरे or in part, of an जातीय, racial, religious, or नेशनल group.
It is पारिभाषित in Article 2 of the Convention on the रोकथाम और दंड of the अपराधों of नरसंहार ( CPPCG ) of 1948 as `` कोई of the following अधिनियमों committed साथ intent to destroy, in whole or in भाग, a national, ethnical, जातिगत or धार्मिक समूह, as ऐसे : हत्या सदस्यों of the समूह ; causing serious bodily or दिमागी harm to सदस्यों of the समूह ; deliberately inflicting on the समूह conditions of life, गणना to लाओ परिचय इसके शारीरिक विनाश in पूरे or in भाग ; imposing उपायों intended to prevent births भीतर the समूह ; [ and ] forcibly transferring children of the समूह to another समूह. ''
Skulls of victims of the rwandan Genocide
the प्रस्तावना to the CPPCG नहीं only राज्य that `` genocide is a crime अंतर्गत international विधि, contrary to the स्पिरिट and aims of the United Nations और condemned by the civilized संसार '', लकिन भी कि `` at सब periods of history नरसंहार रै inflicted ग्रेट नुकसान on humanity ''.
Determining कया ऐतिहासिक कार्यक्रम constitute a नरसंहार and जिससे हैं merely criminal or inhuman behavior is नहीं a clear-cut matter.
in nearly every मामला जहाँ accusations of नरसंहार have परिचालित, partisans of विभिन्न sides have fiercely विवादित the interpretation और विवरण of the इवेंट, प्रायः to the पाइंट of promoting wildly different संस्करण of the तथ्य.
an accusation of genocide is certainly not taken हलके and होगा almost सदा be विवादास्पद.
the following सूची of genocides और alleged genocides should be understood in इस कॉन्टेक्स्ट and can not be regarded as the फाइनल शब्द on ये विषय.

the संयुक्त States of अमेरिका is an ethnically और racially diverse देश as a परिणाम of large-scale immigration इससे अनेक अलग देशों throughout इसके history.
Its chief जल्दी यूरोपीय प्रभाव came from English, स्कॉटिश, वेल्श and Irish settlers of औपनिवेशिक अमेरिका दौरान अंग्रेजों नियम.

Prevalent विचार और आदर्शों कि विकसित domestically, ऐसे as national छुट्टियाँ, uniquely अमरीकी खेल, सैन्य परंपरा, और innovations in the कला और entertainment दे a दमदार भाव of national pride among the population as a whole.
American culture includes दोनो conservative और उदार तत्व, वैज्ञानिक और धार्मिक प्रतिस्पर्धात्मकता, political structures, रिस्क taking and free अभिव्यक्ति, materialist और moral elements.
Despite निश्चित सतत ideological principles ( e.g. व्यक्तिगत, egalitarianism, and आस्था in स्वतंत्रता और लोकतंत्र ), American संस्कृति रै a variety of expressions due to its geographical scale and demographic विविधता.
The लचीलापन of U.S. culture और इसके अत्यधिक symbolic प्रकृति lead कुछ शोधकर्ताओं to categorize अमरीकी culture as a mythic पहचान ; others देखिए it as American exceptionalism.
It भी includes elements that विकसित इससे स्वदेशी अमेरिकी, और अन्य ethnic cultures—most prominently the culture of अफ़्रीकी Americans, cultures इससे लैटिन अमेरिका, और Asian अमरीकी cultures.

Samoan ( Gagana fa'a sāmoa or Gagana sāmoa — आईपीए : ) is the language of the samoan आइलैंड्स, comprising the independent देश of समोआ and the संयुक्त States territory of अमरीकी Samoa.
it is an official language—alongside अंग्रेज़ी —in दोनो jurisdictions.
samoan, a पोलिनेशियाई language, is the first भाषा लिये सबसे of the समोआ आइलैंड्स ' जनसांख्यिकी of परिचय 246,000.
साथ अनेक Samoan लोगों जीना in अन्य देशों, the total number of speakers worldwide is अनुमानित at 370,000.
The भाषा is notable लिये the phonological मतभेद between formal and informal speech as खूब as a ceremonial रूप प्रयुक्त in samoan oratory.
A ग्लूकोज सहिष्णुता परीक्षण is a चिकित्सा test in which glucose is दिए और blood नमूने लिया afterward to determine how जल्दी it is cleared इससे the blood.
the परीक्षण is usually used to परीक्षण लिये मधुमेह, insulin प्रतिरोध, and sometimes प्रतिक्रिया hypoglycemia और acromegaly, or rarer disorders of शर्करा metabolism.
in the सबसे commonly performed संस्करण of the परीक्षण, an oral ग्लूकोज tolerance परीक्षण ( OGTT ), a standard dose of ग्लूकोज is ingested by mouth and रक्त स्तर हैं checked two घंटों बाद.
अनेक विसंगतियाँ of the GTT have महरूम devised over the years लिये various purposes, with अलग मानक doses of ग्लूकोज, अलग रूट of administration, different intervals and durations of sampling, और विभिन्न substances measured in जोड to रक्त ग्लूकोज.

प्रमुख लीग सॉकर ( mls ) is a पेशेवर सॉकर लीग representing the खेल 's उच्चतम स्तर in the United States and कनाडा.
Sanctioned by the संयुक्त राज्य सॉकर Federation ( U.S. सॉकर ), the लीग is रचित of 19 teams — 16 in the U.S. and 3 in Canada.

the legality of कैनबिस varies from देश to country.
Possession of कैनबिस is illegal in सबसे देशों और रै been चूंकि the beginning of फैली cannabis निषेध in the late 1930s.
however, अनेक countries have decriminalized the कब्ज़ा of small quantities of कैनबिस, विशेषकर in उत्तर अमेरिका, South America और Europe.
Furthermore, कब्ज़ा is legal or effectively legal in the नीदरलैंड्स, North कोरियाई और would be in the u.S. states of कोलोराडो and Washington if it were नहीं लिये संघीय विधि, which governs व्यक्तियों in all राज्य.
the medicinal use of कैनबिस is legal in a number of देशों, including कनाडा, the चेक गणतंत्र और इसराईल.
जबकि federal law in the United States bans all बिक्री और कब्ज़ा of कैनबिस, enforcement varies widely at the राज्य level और some states have स्थापित औषधीय मारिजुआना कार्यक्रम in that खण्डन संघीय law ; दो states ( कोलोराडो और वॉशिंगटन ) have repealed उनके कानून prohibiting the recreational उपयोग of cannabis and replaced उन्हें साथ a नियामक शासन, भी contrary to संघीय statute.
कुछ देशों have कानून कि हैं not as vigorously prosecuted as अन्य लकिन, अलावा from the countries that प्रस्ताव access to चिकित्सा मारिजुआना, सबसे देशों have various penalties ranging from lenient to very कठोर.
कुछ infractions are taken more seriously in कुछ देशों than अन्य in regard to the cultivation, use, कब्ज़ा or transfer of कैनबिस लिये recreational use.
a few jurisdictions have lessened दंड for कब्ज़ा of small quantities of cannabis, बनाना it दंडनीय by confiscation and a ठीक, rather than imprisonment.
कुछ क्षेत्राधिकारs/ ड्रग courts उपयोग mandatory उपचार programs for यंग or बारंबार users, साथ स्वतंत्रता इससे narcotic दवाएँ as the लक्ष्य and a few jurisdictions permit कैनबिस use लिये medicinal purposes.
वहीँ are भी changes in a more restrictive दिशा as in कनाडा.
ड्रग परीक्षण to detect cannabis हैं increasingly आम in अनेक देशों और have resulted in कारावास वाक्य and लोगों खोने उनके jobs.
however, सरल possession can carry long jail वाक्य in कुछ देशों, विशेषकर in parts of ईस्ट Asia and southeast एशिया जहाँ the बिक्री of कैनबिस may lead to a sentence of life in prison or भी execution.
in cardiovascular physiology, ejection भिन्न ( EF ) represents the आयतनी भिन्न of रक्त उत्तेजित आउट of the ventricle ( heart ) साथ each दिल ताल or cardiac cycle.
it can be applied to either the right ventricle जिससे ejects via the pulmonary वाल्व into the pulmonary परिसंचरण or the बाएँ ventricle जिससे ejects via the aortic वाल्व into the प्रणालीगत परिसंचरण.
इमेजिंग of the physiology of the mammalian दिल is the आर्ट कि allows meaningful गणितीय अभिव्यक्ति defining EF.
Noninvasive cardiac इमेजिंग रै become a worldwide यूटिलिटी enabling पढ़ाई of cardiac performance reproducibly और inexpensively.
सरलीकृत, ejection भिन्न is a mathematical उत्पाद allowed by हृदय imaging.
As a गणितीय पद, Ejection भिन्न is an एक्सटेंशन of the work of Adolph फिक in हृदय आउटपुट.
Dedicated प्रौद्योगिकी ऐसे as इकोकार्डियोग्राफी, Computed टोमोग्राफी, Magnetic Resonance Imaging और MUGA scanning have definitively अनुमत clinically प्रासंगिक mathematics regarding ischemia, Congenital दिल बीमारी and Heart Failure.
राज्य Route 14 ( sr 14 ) is a north–south state highway in the U.S. राज्य of कैलिफ़ोर्निया, largely in the Mojave मरुस्थल.
The दक्षिणी portion of the राजमार्ग is हस्ताक्षरित as the Antelope घाटी फ्रीवे.
the route connects Interstate 5, or Golden State फ्रीवे, near Santa clarita and साथ u.S. रूट 395 near Inyokern.
legislatively, the route extends दक्षिण of i-5 to राज्य Route 1 in the प्रशांत palisades क्षेत्रफल of लॉस Angeles, however the portion दक्षिण of the जंक्शन साथ i-5 रै नहीं महरूम constructed.
the southern भाग of the constructed रूट is a busy commuter freeway serving और connecting the communities of सांता clarita, palmdale और lancaster साथ the बाकी of the Greater लॉस Angeles area.
the northern portion, इससे Vincent ( south of Palmdale ) to Route 395, is legislatively named the Aerospace Highway, as the राजमार्ग serves एडवर्ड्स एयर फ़ोर्स Base, एकबार एक of the प्राथमिक लैंडिंग strips लिये NASA 's Space Shuttle.
This खण्ड is ग्रामीण, following the लकीर between the hot mojave मरुस्थल और the forming सिएरा नेवाडा पहाड़ दायरा.
Most of रूट 14 is loosely paralleled by a main लकीर of the दक्षिणी Pacific Railroad, प्रयुक्त लिये the Antelope घाटी Line of the metrolink commuter रेल प्रणाली as well as a connection between लॉस Angeles और the California सेंट्रल Valley via tehachapi pass.
linked with us 395, इस सड़क connects लॉस Angeles साथ ऐसे स्थान as मैमथ Mountain, मोनो झील, Yosemite नेशनल Park और Reno, Nevada.
Route 14 थी भाग of u.S. रूट 6 prior to truncation in 1964, जब u.S. 6 was a coast-to-coast रूट इससे Long बीच to Provincetown, मैसाचुसेट्स.
the non-freeway खण्ड of sr 14 इससे Silver महारानी सड़क north of rosamond to mojave is ज्ञात as सिएरा Highway, as is the old routing between अंतरराज्यीय 5 and चांदी Queen Road where sr 14 रै महरूम स्थानांतरित to a नए freeway संरेखण.
Portions of Route 14 remain signed साथ names associated with us 6, including Midland Trail, Theodore रूज़वेल्ट राजमार्ग and Grand Army of the गणतंत्र राजमार्ग.
This रूट is भाग of the कैलिफ़ोर्निया फ्रीवे और Expressway System.
Blindness is the condition of lacking विज़ुअल बोध due to physiological or neurological कारकों.
Various तराजू have महरूम developed to describe the extent of दृष्टि घाटा और define blindness.
कुल दृष्टिहीनता is the पूरा lack of रूप and विज़ुअल light बोध और is clinically recorded as nlp, an संक्षिप्त लिये `` no light बोध. ''
दृष्टिहीनता is frequently प्रयुक्त to describe severe विज़ुअल impairment साथ vision.
those described as having तभी लाइट बोध have no अधिक sight than the क्षमता to बताना light इससे अंधेरा और the सामान्य दिशा of a लाइट सोर्स.
to determine जिससे people may need खास सहायता क्युकी of उनके visual disabilities, विभिन्न governmental jurisdictions have प्रतिपादित अधिक जटिल परिभाषाएं referred to as legal दृष्टिहीनता.
in उत्तर अमेरिका और सबसे of Europe, विधिक दृष्टिहीनता is defined as विज़ुअल तीक्ष्णता ( vision ) of 20/200 ( 6/60 ) or कम in the better नजर with बेहतरीन सुधार संभावित.
इस अर्थात् कि a legally अँधा व्यक्तिगत would have to स्टैंड from an ऑब्जेक्ट to see it—with corrective lenses —with the वही उपाधि of clarity as a normally sighted व्यक्ति could इससे.
in अनेक क्षेत्रों, people साथ average acuity जो nonetheless have a विज़ुअल फ़ील्ड of less than 20 डिग्री ( the norm being 180 degrees ) हैं also classified as होने legally अँधा.
Approximately ten प्रतिशत of those deemed legally अँधा, by any माप, have no vision.
The बाकी have some vision, इससे light बोध अलोन to अपेक्षाकृत शुभ तीक्ष्णता.
Low दृष्टि is sometimes प्रयुक्त to describe विज़ुअल acuities इससे 20/70 to 20/200.
by the 10th Revision of the जो International सांख्यिकीय Classification of रोगों, Injuries and कल्याणकारी of मौत, low दृष्टि is defined as visual तीक्ष्णता of कम than 20/60 ( 6/18 ), but बराबर to or बेहतर than 20/200 ( 6/60 ), or सम्बन्धित विज़ुअल field घाटा to कम than 20 डिग्री, in the बेहतर नजर with best possible सुधार.
Blindness is पारिभाषित as visual तीक्ष्णता of कम than 20/400 ( 6/120 ), or corresponding visual field घाटा to less than 10 डिग्री, in the बेहतर नजर साथ बेहतरीन संभावित सुधार.
Blind लोगों with undamaged eyes may still पंजीकरण लाइट non-visually लिये the purpose of circadian entrainment to the 24-hour light/dark साईकिल.
लाइट signals for इस purpose travel through the retinohypothalamic tract और हैं नहीं affected by optic nerve damage परे जहाँ the retinohypothalamic tract exits.

They line कैविटी कि हैं उजागर to the external पर्यावरण and आतंरिक organs.

केक is a form of bread or bread-like food.
In its modern forms, it is typically a मीठी baked मिठाई.
In its oldest फ़ॉर्म, cakes यहूद normally fried breads or cheesecakes, and सामान्यतः था a डिस्क आकार.
determining whether a given food चाहिए be वर्गीकृत as ब्रैड, केक, or पेस्ट्री can be difficult.
आधुनिक केक, विशेषकर परत cakes, सामान्यतः contain a combination of आटा, शुगर, eggs, and butter or आयल, साथ some varieties also requiring द्रव ( typically मिल्क or जल ) और leavening एजेंटों ( such as खमीर or बेकिंग चूर्ण ).
flavorful ingredients like फल purées, nuts, सूखी or candied fruit, or extracts are often added, और numerous substitutions लिये the primary ingredients are possible.
cakes हैं often filled साथ फल preserves or dessert sauces ( जैसे pastry मलाई ), आइस्ड साथ buttercream or अन्य icings, और सजा साथ marzipan, piped सीमायें or candied फल.
Cake is प्रायः the मिठाई of choice for meals at ceremonial occasions, particularly weddings, वर्षगांठ, और जन्मदिन.
वहीँ हैं अनगिनत केक recipes ; कुछ हैं bread-like, कुछ rich and elaborate, और अनेक are centuries old.
Cake बनाना is no longer a complicated कार्यविधि ; while at one समय considerable मजदूर गई into cake making ( particularly the whisking of egg foams ), बेकिंग equipment और दिशानिर्देश have महरूम सरलीकृत so कि भी the सबसे amateur कुक may bake a केक.

Public नीति is the principled मार्गदर्शिका to कार्रवाई लिया by the administrative कार्यपालिका शाखाओं of the राज्य with लिहाज़ to a क्लास of issues in a manner consistent with विधि और संस्थागत customs.
In general, the न्यास is the pertinent national और substantial संवैधानिक law और implementing विधान such as the US Federal कोड.
further substrates शामिल दोनो न्यायिक interpretations और regulations which हैं generally प्राधिकृत by legislation.
अन्य विद्वानों define it as a system of `` पाठ्यक्रम of action, नियामक उपायों, कानून, और funding priorities concerning a given टॉपिक promulgated by a governmental entity or its प्रतिनिधि. ''
Public policy is commonly समाविष्ट `` in constitutions, विधान acts, and न्यायिक निर्णय. ''
in the United राज्य, इस अवधारणा refers नहीं only to the परिणाम of policies, लकिन अधिक broadly to the decision-making and analysis of सरकारी decisions.
as an academic अनुशासन, पब्लिक नीति is studied by professors और students at पब्लिक नीति schools of प्रमुख विश्वविद्यालयों throughout the country.
The u.S. पेशेवर association of पब्लिक policy practitioners, researchers, विद्वानों, and students is the संघ for पब्लिक नीति Analysis और Management.
पाचन is the mechanical और रासायनिक विश्लेषण of खाना into smaller components that हैं अधिक easily absorbed into a रक्त stream, for उदाहरण.
पाचन is a रूप of catabolism : a विश्लेषण of विशाल खाना अणुओं to छोटी ones.
जब खाना enters the mouth, पाचन of the खाना starts by the कार्रवाई of mastication, a रूप of mechanical पाचन, and the wetting सम्पर्क of लार.
लार, a liquid secreted by the salivary ग्रंथियों, contains salivary amylase, an एंजाइम जिससे starts the पाचन of starch in the food.
बाद undergoing mastication and starch पाचन, the food will be in the form of a small, round slurry mass पुकारा a bolus.
it will then सफर down the esophagus और into the पेट by the कार्रवाई of peristalsis.
gastric रस in the पेट starts प्रोटीन पाचन.
Gastric रस मुख्यतः contains hydrochloric acid और pepsin.
as these दो रसायन may damage the पेट wall, mucus is स्रावित by the stomach, providing a slimy layer कि acts as a शील्ड विरूद्ध the damaging प्रभाव of the chemicals.
At the वही समय प्रोटीन पाचन is occurring, mechanical mixing occurs by peristalsis, जिससे हैं लहरें of muscular contractions that move साथ the stomach वॉल.
This allows the mass of खाना to further मिक्सर साथ the digestive enzymes.
After कुछ समय ( typically an घंटा or two in humans, 4–6 घंटों in कुत्तो, somewhat shorter duration in house cats ), the resulting मोटा liquid is called chyme.
When the pyloric sphincter वाल्व opens, chyme enters the duodenum जहाँ it mixes साथ digestive एंजाइमों from the pancreas, और तब passes through the small आंत, in जिससे पाचन continues.
When the chyme is fully digested, it is अवशोषित into the रक्त.
95 % of अवशोषण of nutrients occurs in the छोटी आंत.
Water and खनिज हैं reabsorbed वापस into the रक्त in the colon ( विशाल intestine ) जहाँ the ph is थोड़ा अम्लीय परिचय 5.6 ~ 6.9.
Some vitamins, ऐसे as biotin and vitamin K ( K2MK7 ) उत्पादित by जीवाणु in the कोलन हैं also अवशोषित into the blood in the कोलन.
बर्बाद material is eliminated इससे the मलाशय during शौच.
हेनरी viii ( 28 June 1491 – 28 जनवरी 1547 ) was किंग of इंग्लैण्ड from 21 अप्रैल 1509 until his death.
he थी रब, और बाद king, of Ireland, as well as continuing the नाममात्र अर्जी by the अंग्रेज़ी monarchs to the किंगडम of France.
हेनरी थी the second monarch of the ट्यूडर dynasty, succeeding his father, हेनरी सात.
besides उसके छह विवाह, हेनरी viii is known लिये his भूमिका in the separation of the गिरिजाघर of England इससे the रोमन कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर.
हेनरी 's struggles साथ रोम led to the विरह of the Church of England इससे papal authority, the विच्छेद of the monasteries, and उसके अपना establishment as the Supreme सिर of the Church of England.
yet he remained a believer in core कैथोलिक theological teachings, भी after उसके excommunication from the रोमन कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर.
Henry oversaw the विधिक संघ of इंग्लैण्ड and वेल्स साथ the कानून in वेल्स Acts 1535 और 1542.
in 1513, the नई किंग अलाइड with the पावन रोमन सम्राट, maximillian i, और invaded फ़्रांस in 1513 साथ a large, well-equipped army, लकिन हासिल छोटी at a considerable financial cost.
maximillian, लिये उसके भाग, used the अंग्रेज़ी invasion to his अपना ends, और इस prejudiced इंग्लैण्ड 's ability to शिकस्त the French.
This foray would prove the start of an obsession लिये Henry, जो invaded again in 1544.
इस समय, हेनरी 's forces captured the महत्वपूर्ण नगर of boulogne, but again the पावन रोमन Emperor, Charles V, समर्थित Henry तभी as long as he needed to and इंग्लैण्ड, strained by the विशाल लागत of the war, ransomed the city वापस for peace.
उसके contemporaries considered Henry in उसके prime to be an आकर्षक, educated and संपन्नता किंग, और he रै been described as `` एक of the सबसे charismatic शासकों to बैठना on the अंग्रेज़ी throne ''.
Besides सत्ताधारी साथ निरपेक्ष power, he भी engaged himself as an लेखक and composer.
His ख्वाहिश to provide इंग्लैण्ड साथ a पुरूष वारिस – जिससे stemmed partly from निजी वैनिटी और partly because he believed a बेटी होता be असमर्थ to consolidate the Tudor dynasty and the नाजुक peace that existed following the Wars of the गुलाब – led to the two बाते for which हेनरी is most remembered : his six विवाह and the अंग्रेज़ी reformation.
Henry became morbidly मोटे and his health suffered, contributing to his death in 1547.
he is अक्सर characterised in उसके later जीवन as a lustful, egotistical, harsh, and असुरक्षित king.
bongos ( Spanish : bongó ) हैं an afro-cuban percussion यंत्र.
The ड्रम are of अलग आकार : the larger drum is पुकारा in स्पेनी the hembra ( मादा ) और the smaller the मर्दाना ( male ).
They हैं membranophones, or instruments कि बनाएँ ध्वनि by a vibration of a stretched झिल्ली.
Different धार्मिक groups include अलग किताबे in their biblical canons, in varying orders, और sometimes divide or combine किताबे, or incorporate additional material into canonical books.
ईसाई bibles range from the sixty-six किताबे of the प्रोटोस्टेंट canon to the eighty-one किताबे of the Ethiopian परंपरागत tewahedo गिरिजाघर canon.
The यहूदी बाइबल, or tanakh, contains twenty-four books विभाजित into तीन भाग ; the पाँच books of the Torah ( `` teaching '' or `` law '' ), the nevi'im ( `` prophets '' ), और the Ketuvim ( `` writings '' ).
the पहला भाग of ईसाई Bibles is the बूढ़ा वसीयत, जिससे contains, at minimum, the twenty-four किताबे of the यहूदी बाइबल विभाजित into thirty-nine किताबे और ordered differently from the यहूदी बाइबल.
the कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर और Eastern ईसाई churches भी थाम certain deuterocanonical books and passages to be भाग of the Old Testament canon.
the दूसरी part is the New Testament, containing twenty-seven books ; the चार canonical gospels, अधिनियमों of the रसूलों, twenty-one epistles or अक्षर और the Book of रहस्योद्घाटन.
The पूर्वी परंपरागत, प्राच्य Orthodox और Eastern कैथोलिक चर्च may have minor मतभेद in उनके सूचियाँ of स्वीकृत किताबे.
the सूची given here लिये these churches is the सबसे समावेशी : if at least one Eastern गिरिजाघर स्वीकृत the किताब it is शामिल यहाँ.
The नेशनल ध्वज of the संयुक्त राज्य of अमेरिका, often बस referred to as the American flag, consists of तेरह equal आड़ा धारियाँ of रेड ( शीर्ष और नीचे ) प्रत्यावर्ती साथ white, with a blue rectangle in the कैण्टन ( referred to specifically as the `` union '' ) bearing पचास small, white, five-pointed stars arranged in नौ ऑफसेट आड़ा rows of छह stars ( top and नीचे ) alternating साथ पंक्ति of पाँच सितारों.
The 50 stars on the flag represent the 50 states of the संयुक्त States of अमेरिका and the 13 धारियाँ represent the तेरह अंग्रेजों colonies that घोषित स्वतंत्रता इससे the किंगडम of ग्रेट ब्रिटेन और became the पहला राज्य in the संघ.
nicknames लिये the ध्वज शामिल the `` सितारों and धारियाँ '', `` Old महिमा ``, और `` The star-spangled ध्वज. ''
dred Scott v. sandford,, भी known as the Dred Scott निर्णय, was a landmark decision by the U.S. Supreme Court.
it बना दो main rulings.
The first सत्ताधारी was that African-Americans यहूद not नागरिकों, and इसलिए had no standing to मुकदमा in संघीय court.
the दूसरी सत्ताधारी थी कि the federal government था no power to regulate slavery in कोई territory acquired subsequent to the creation of the संयुक्त राज्य.
Given the पहला सत्ताधारी, सबसे विद्वानों and अनेक contemporary राजनैतिक आंकड़े ( सहित the नेतृत्व of the then-new रिपब्लिकन Party ) considered कि the दूसरी सत्ताधारी was नहीं binding यही, but mere कहावत.
The युक्तिसंगत of the परम् Court regarding the jurisdictional सत्ताधारी implied कि people of African descent ( दोनो slave और फ़्री ) यहूद नहीं सुरक्षित by the Constitution and were नहीं u.S. नागरिकों.
Since passage of the 14th amendment to the u.S. संविधान, दोनो rulings are superseded और no longer valid precedent.
nonetheless, the मामला retains historical significance as it is widely regarded as the worst decision ever बना by the परम् अदालत.
The राय of the court, written by Chief इंसाफ रोजर B. taney, stirred debate.
The निर्णय थी 7–2, और प्रत्येक इंसाफ besides taney wrote a पृथक concurrence or dissent.
For the पहला समय चूंकि marbury v. Madison, the अदालत आयोजित an अधिनियम of कॉंग्रेस to be unconstitutional.
Dred Scott, an African-American slave, था asked a United राज्य सर्किट Court to award him उसके स्वतंत्रता क्युकी he and उसके निपुण had resided in a राज्य ( इलिनोइस ) and a territory ( Wisconsin Territory ) जहाँ गुलामी था महरूम बैन.
Chief इंसाफ Roger taney, writing लिये the अदालत, आयोजित कि स्कॉट, as a व्यक्ति of अफ़्रीकी ancestry, थी not a citizen of the संयुक्त राज्य and इसलिए had no right to sue in federal अदालत.
इस पकड़कर was contrary to the अभ्यास of numerous राज्य at the समय, विशेषकर फ़्री राज्य, जहाँ फ़्री अश्वेतों किया in फैक्ट enjoy the rights of citizens, such as the right to vote and hold public office.
in कया is sometimes माना mere obiter कहावत, the अदालत गई on to थाम कि Congress था no प्राधिकार to prohibit गुलामी in संघीय territories because slaves हैं निजी property और the पांचवां amendment to the संविधान protects प्रॉपर्टी owners विरूद्ध deprivation of उनके प्रॉपर्टी without due प्रक्रम of विधि.
in reaching इस decision, Taney था hoped to settle the growing controversy surrounding slavery in the United राज्य, लकिन it था the विपरीत प्रभाव.
the निर्णय थी fiercely debated आरपार the country, as शायद बेहतरीन सरंचनाओं by the Lincoln–Douglas debates of 1858.
अब्राहम Lincoln, the second-ever रिपब्लिकन nominee लिये अध्यक्ष, थी समर्थ to जीत the अध्यक्षीय चुनाव in 1860 ; the stopping of the further expansion of गुलामी थी a कुंजी रिपब्लिकन पार्टी यों.
the decision निभाई an महत्वपूर्ण role in the timing of राज्य secession और the सिविल War, although it is चरम to कह the निर्णय `` caused '' the युद्ध.
The decision is acknowledged लिये the influential भूमिका it played in altering the नेशनल political लैंडस्केप : it is credited with शुभारंभ Abraham lincoln’s national राजनैतिक करियर और ultimately allowing for उसके election.
हालांकि the परम् Court रै never explicitly overruled the dred स्कॉट मामला, the अदालत stated in the Slaughter-House Cases that at least एक part of it था already been overruled by the Fourteenth amendment in 1868, which begins by stating, `` सब persons born or देशीयकृत in the United राज्य, और subject to the क्षेत्राधिकार thereof, हैं नागरिकों of the संयुक्त States और of the State wherein they reside. ''
To जिससे the Court noted:
the पहला अवलोकन we have to make on इस clause is, that it puts at rest दोनो the सवाल which we stated to have महरूम the विषय of मतभेद of राय.
It declares that व्यक्तियों may be citizens of the संयुक्त States बगैर regard to उनके नागरिकता of a particular राज्य, और it overturns the dred Scott निर्णय by making all व्यक्तियों born भीतर the संयुक्त राज्य और subject to its क्षेत्राधिकार citizens of the United States.

A जीवविज्ञानी is a वैज्ञानिक जो अध्ययन जीना जीवों और उनके relationship to their environment.

the संयुक्त राज्य is currently ranked पहला in the fiba संसार Rankings.

in 1996, 2000, 2008, और 2012 the यूएसए again captured gold medals.

the 2004 Summer ओलम्पिक टोली खोया तीन games on its way to a कांस्य medal, a record that represented more नुकसान in a सिंगल साल than the country 's ओलम्पिक टीमों had suffered in सब previous olympiads संयुक्त.

A stalagmite ( or ; from the यूनानी σταλαγμίτης - stalagmitês, from σταλαγμίας - stalagmias, `` छोड़ने, trickling '' ) is a प्रकार of speleothem कि उदय इससे the मंजिल of a चूना cave due to the टपकता of mineralized समाधान और the deposition of कैल्सियम carbonate.
इस stalagmite गठन occurs तभी अंतर्गत certain ph शर्तें भीतर the underground cavern.
the सम्बन्धित गठन on the ceiling of a गुफा is ज्ञात as a stalactite.
if ये formations grow साथ, the result is ज्ञात as a कालम.
the हॉल of दिग्गज in the carlsbad Caverns
stalagmites चाहिए सामान्यतः नहीं be छुआ, since the चट्टान buildup is formed by खनिज precipitating out of the जल समाधान onto the बूढ़ा सतह ; स्किन oils can alter the सतह where the खनिज जल होगा चिपकी, thus affecting the growth of the गठन.
oils and मैल from इंसान सम्पर्क can also stain the formation and change इसके रंग permanently.
समान structures can भी रूप in लावा tubes, संबद्ध with कुछ types of lavacicles, although the यांत्रिकी of गठन is very different.
stalactites and stalagmites can भी form on कंक्रीट ceilings और floors, हालांकि वे रूप much अधिक rapidly there than in the प्राकृतिक गुफा पर्यावरण.
the largest stalagmite in the संसार is high and is located in the गुफा of cueva Martin infierno, क्यूबा.
in the Zagros kyu of दक्षिण Iran, लगभग इससे the ancient city of bishapur, in the Shapur cave on the fourth of पाँच terraces stands the 3rd सदी CE statue of shapur I, second शासक of the सासानी साम्राज्य.

Gringo (,, ) is a slang स्पेनी और पुर्तगाली शब्द प्रयुक्त in Ibero-America, to denote foreigners, प्रायः from the संयुक्त States.
the term can be लागू to किसी who is दरअसल a foreigner, or it can denote a strong association or assimilation into विदेशी ( particularly us ) समाज और संस्कृति.
in स्पेनी it does नहीं have a ऋणात्मक connotation.
Roger axtell, a सफर तहज़ीब विशेषज्ञ, टीप that `` [ t ] he word gringo is नहीं necessarily a ख़राब शब्द.
it is slang but is अपमानजनक तभी in its उपयोग and कॉन्टेक्स्ट. ''
the शब्द थी प्रयुक्त in Spain long before it crossed the अटलांटिक to denote विदेशी, non-native अध्यक्षों of Spanish.
The great श्वेत shark, Carcharodon carcharias, also ज्ञात as the great श्वेत, श्वेत सूचक, white शार्क, or श्वेत मौत, is a प्रजाति of विशाल lamniform शार्क which can be मिला in the तटीय सतह waters of all the प्रमुख oceans.
the ग्रेट white शार्क is मुख्यतः ज्ञात for its आकार, with the largest individuals ज्ञात to have approached or exceeded in लंबाई, और in वज़न.
इस शार्क पहुँच its maturity around 15 years of age और can have a life स्पैन of over 30 सालो.
The ग्रेट white shark is arguably the संसार 's largest ज्ञात extant macropredatory fish, और is एक of the प्राथमिक परभक्षी of marine स्तनधारियों.
It is also ज्ञात to शिकार upon a किस्में of अन्य समुद्री पशु, including fish and seabirds.
it is the तभी known surviving species of इसके genus carcharodon, and is क्रमित first in having the सबसे attacks on इंसानो.
