the संयुक्त States Armed शक्तियां are the military शक्तियां of the United राज्य of अमेरिका.
They consist of the फौज, नेवी, समुद्री Corps, Air फ़ोर्स, and Coast गार्ड.
The U.S. रै a strong परंपरा of civilian control of the military.
The अध्यक्ष is the सैन्य 's overall head, और helps रूप सैन्य नीति साथ the u.S. Department of Defense ( DoD ), a संघीय कार्यपालिका विभाग, एक्टिंग as the principal organ by जिससे सैन्य policy is carried आउट.
The DoD is headed by the Secretary of रक्षा, who is a civilian and Cabinet सदस्य.
The Defense Secretary is second in the military 's कड़ी of कमांड, just नीचे the अध्यक्ष, and serves as the प्रिंसिपल सहायक to the President in all dod-related matters.
to निर्देशांक सैन्य कार्रवाई साथ diplomacy, the President रै an सलाहकार National Security परिषद headed by a National सुरक्षा सलाहकार.
दोनो the अध्यक्ष and Secretary of रक्षा are advised by a seven-member संयुक्त Chiefs of स्टाफ, which includes the सिर of प्रत्येक of the रक्षा विभाग 's सेवा शाखाओं as well as the मुख्य of the नेशनल गार्ड Bureau.
नेतृत्व is provided by the अध्यक्ष of the Joint Chiefs of Staff and the वाइस अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त chiefs of स्टाफ.
The कमांडेंट of the Coast गार्ड is नहीं a सदस्य of the संयुक्त chiefs of Staff.
सब of the branches कार्य together दौरान परिचालन और संयुक्त मिशन, under the Unified combatant कमांड, अंतर्गत the प्राधिकार of the सचिव of रक्षा with the exception of the coast Guard.
The coast गार्ड जलप्रपात अंतर्गत the प्रशासन of the विभाग of मातृभूमि Security और receives its operational आदेश इससे the सचिव of Homeland Security.
the Coast Guard may be transferred to the विभाग of the नेवी by the अध्यक्ष or Congress दौरान a time of युद्ध.
All five armed services हैं among the seven uniformed services of the United States ; the others हैं the u.S. पब्लिक Health Service commissioned corps और the National Oceanic and वायुमंडलीय Administration commissioned Corps.
From the time of its inception, the military played a निर्णायक भूमिका in the history of the संयुक्त States.
a भाव of नेशनल unity and identity was forged as a परिणाम of विजय in the First Barbary War and the Second Barbary War.
भी so, the Founders were संदिग्ध of a permanent military फ़ोर्स और नहीं जबतक the outbreak of संसार युद्ध II किया a विशाल खड़ा फौज become officially established.
The National Security अधिनियम of 1947, अपनाया following संसार युद्ध II और during the ठंडा युद्ध 's onset, created the आधुनिक U.S. सैन्य framework ; the Act मिलाया previously cabinet-level विभाग of युद्ध और the विभाग of the Navy into the नेशनल सैन्य Establishment ( renamed the विभाग of रक्षा in 1949 ), headed by the सचिव of रक्षा ; और created the विभाग of the एयर Force और National Security Council.
the u.S. सैन्य is one of the largest militaries in terms of क्रमांक of कर्मियों.
it draws its manpower इससे a विशाल pool of सशुल्क स्वयंसेवक ; हालांकि conscription रै been प्रयुक्त in the पास्ट in विभिन्न टाइम्स of दोनो युद्ध और सलाम, it रै नहीं been प्रयुक्त चूंकि 1972.
as of 2013, the u.S. spends about $ 554.2 billion annually to fund इसके सैन्य शक्तियां, और appropriates लगभग $ 88.5 अरब to निधि विदेशी आकस्मिकता Operations.
put साथ, the u.S. constitutes roughly 43 प्रतिशत of the world 's सैन्य expenditures.
the U.S. हथियारबंद शक्तियां as a whole possess large quantities of उन्नत और powerful उपकरण, साथ साथ फैली अवस्थिति of forces around the संसार, giving उन्हें significant सामर्थ्य in दोनो defense and power प्रक्षेप.
स्वतंत्रता of वाक is the राजनैतिक right to communicate one 's राय और ideas using one 's body and प्रॉपर्टी to anyone who is willing to receive them.
The पद स्वतंत्रता of अभिव्यक्ति is sometimes used synonymously, लकिन includes कोई act of seeking, receiving and imparting सूचना or विचार, regardless of the मीडियम प्रयुक्त.
In अभ्यास, the right to स्वतंत्रता of speech is नहीं निरपेक्ष in any country and the सही is commonly विषय to limitations, as साथ मानहानि, बदनामी, obscenity, राजद्रोह ( सहित, लिये उदाहरण inciting जातीय द्वेष ), कापीराइट उल्लंघन, रहस्योद्घाटन of information that is वर्गीकृत or वरना.
The right to freedom of expression is पहचाना as a human सही अंतर्गत आलेख 19 of the Universal घोषणा of इंसान Rights और recognized in international इंसान अधिकारों law in the International वचन on Civil and राजनैतिक अधिकारों ( iccpr ).
आलेख 19 of the iccpr राज्य कि `` [ e ] veryone shall have the सही to hold राय बगैर हस्तक्षेप '' और `` everyone shall have the सही to freedom of अभिव्यक्ति ; इस right shall शामिल स्वतंत्रता to seek, प्राप्त और impart सूचना और ideas of all kinds, regardless of frontiers, either orally, in लिखने or in print, in the रूप of art, or through any अन्य media of उसके चुनाव ''.
आलेख 19 goes on to कह that the कसरत of ये rights carries `` special कर्तव्य and responsibilities `` and may `` therefore be subject to निश्चित restrictions '' when जरुरी `` [ f ] or आदर of the अधिकारों or reputation of others '' or `` [ f ] or the protection of national security or of पब्लिक order ( order पब्लिक ), or of पब्लिक स्वास्थ्य or नैतिकता ''.
स्वतंत्रता of वाक may be legally curtailed in some religious विधिक प्रणालियों और in धर्मनिरपेक्ष jurisdictions जहाँ it is मिला to cause धार्मिक offense, such as the British Racial and Religious द्वेष अधिनियम 2006.
the बिग Bang Theory लोगो.
The बिग बंग सिद्धान्त is an American कॉमेडी television श्रेणी निर्मित और executive उत्पादित by Chuck lorre और विधेयक prady.
जैसे the name of the श्रेणी itself, साथ the exception of the पहला episode— '' Pilot '' —episode शीर्षक of the Big बंग Theory सदा start with `` the '' और resemble the नाम of a वैज्ञानिक principle, theory or experiment, whimsically referencing a प्लाट point or quirk.
, 133 एपीसोड have aired.
the बिग बंग सिद्धान्त रै महरूम नवीनीकृत for a seventh ऋतु.
Dwight दाउद `` Ike '' आइज़नहावर ( सुनाया, ; October 14, 1890 – कूच 28, 1969 ) थी the 34th अध्यक्ष of the United States इससे 1953 until 1961.
he had previously महरूम a five-star general in the संयुक्त States फौज दौरान संसार युद्ध ii and served as परम् कमांडर of the Allied Forces in यूरोपीय ; he था responsibility for planning और supervising the invasion of North अफ़्रीकी in आपरेशन मशाल in 1942–43 and the कामयाब invasion of France और Germany in 1944–45 from the Western Front.
In 1951, he became the first परम् commander of NATO.
आइज़नहावर थी of पेन्सिलवेनिया डच ancestry और थी reared in a large परिवार in कान्सास by अभिभावक साथ a robust कार्य ethic और धार्मिक पृष्ठभूमि.
As one of छह sons, he थी conditioned by a प्रतिस्पर्धी माहौल जिससे instilled self-reliance.
he attended और ग्रैजुएट इससे वेस्ट पाइंट and बाद married and था two बेटे.
After संसार युद्ध II, आइज़नहावर served as फौज मुख्य of स्टाफ अंतर्गत अध्यक्ष हैरी S. ट्रूमैन, then assumed the पोस्ट of President at Columbia विश्वविद्यालयों.
Eisenhower डाला the 1952 अध्यक्षीय रेस as a Republican to counter the non-interventionism of सीनेटर Robert A. Taft और to crusade against `` Communism, Korea and भ्रष्टाचार ''.
He won by a भूस्खलन, defeating डेमोक्रेट adlai stevenson and ending दो दशकों of the New सौदे Coalition.
In the पहला year of उसके प्रेसिडेंसी, आइज़नहावर अपदस्थ the leader of इरान in the 1953 ईरानी तख्तापलट d'état and प्रयुक्त nuclear खतरे to conclude the कोरियाई युद्ध with China.
उसके नई Look नीति of nuclear deterrence gave प्रधानता to inexpensive नाभिकीय हथियार while reducing the funding for conventional सैन्य forces ; the लक्ष्य थी to रखना दबाव on the सोवियत Union and reduce federal deficits.
In 1954, आइज़नहावर first articulated the domino सिद्धान्त in his वर्णन of the threat प्रस्तुत by the spread of communism.
The Congress agreed to उसके request in 1955 लिये the formosa Resolution, which सक्रिय उसे to prevent चाइनीज कम्युनिस्ट aggression against Chinese nationalists और स्थापित the u.S. नीति of defending ताईवान.
जब the Soviets शुभारम्भ Sputnik in 1957, he था to खेल catch-up in the स्पेस race.
आइज़नहावर मजबूर Israel, the UK, और फ़्रांस to समाप्त उनके आक्रमण of Egypt दौरान the स्वेज संकट of 1956.
In 1958, he sent 15,000 US सैनिकों to लेबनान to prevent the pro-western सरकारी इससे falling to a Nasser -inspired क्रान्ति.
Near the end of his term, उसके efforts to set up a समिट बैठक with the soviets collapsed क्युकी of the u-2 घटना.
On the domestic सामने, he covertly opposed जोसेफ मैकार्थी and contributed to the समाप्त of McCarthyism by खुलकर invoking the modern विस्तारित version of कार्यपालिका विशेषाधिकार.
He otherwise left सबसे राजनैतिक कार्यकलाप to his वाइस अध्यक्ष, Richard निक्सन.
he थी a मॉडरेट रूढ़िवादी who जारी नई सौदे एजेंसियों और विस्तारित Social सुरक्षा.
Among उसके enduring नवप्रवर्तनों, he शुभारम्भ the Interstate राजमार्ग प्रणाली ; the रक्षा उन्नत शोध प्रोजेक्ट एजेंसी ( DARPA ), जिससे led to the अंतरजाल, among अनेक invaluable outputs ; the National aeronautics और स्पेस Administration ( NASA ), ड्राइविंग शांतिपूर्ण डिस्कवरी in space ; the स्थापना of strong विज्ञान शिक्षा via the नेशनल रक्षा शिक्षा Act ; और प्रोत्साहित peaceful use of नाभिकीय power via amendments to the परमाणु Energy Act.
In सोशल नीति, he sent federal सैनिकों to छोटी चट्टान, अरकंसास, लिये the पहला समय चूंकि पुनर्निर्माण to enforce संघीय अदालत orders to desegregate पब्लिक schools.
he also हस्ताक्षरित सिविल rights legislation in 1957 and 1960 to protect the सही to vote.
He implemented desegregation of the armed forces in two सालो और बना पाँच नियुक्ति to the Supreme अदालत.
He was the पहला term-limited अध्यक्ष in accordance साथ the 22nd amendment.
Eisenhower 's दो शर्तें were शांतिपूर्ण ones for the सबसे भाग और देखी considerable आर्थिक समृद्धि मगर for a शार्प मंदी in 1958–59.
आइज़नहावर is often क्रमित अत्यधिक among the U.S. Presidents.
एयर Force एक is the official एयर ट्रैफ़िक कंट्रोल कॉल चिह्न of a United राज्य एयर Force aircraft carrying the President of the United राज्य.
in common parlance the पद refers to those Air फ़ोर्स वायुयान specifically designed, निर्मित, and प्रयुक्त लिये the purpose of transporting the अध्यक्ष.
the Presidential वायुयान is a prominent symbol of the American प्रेसिडेंसी and इसके power.
The idea of designating विशिष्ट सैन्य वायुयान to transport the अध्यक्ष arose in 1943, जब officials of the United राज्य फौज एयर शक्तियां – the पूर्ववर्ती to the u.S. Air फ़ोर्स – became concerned with relying on वाणिज्यिक airlines to हस्तांतरण the President.
a c-87 Liberator Express थी reconfigured लिये use as a अध्यक्षीय हस्तांतरण ; however, it was अस्वीकृत by the रहस्य सेवा amid concerns over the aircraft 's सुरक्षा रिकार्ड.
a c-54 skymaster थी तब परिवर्तित for अध्यक्षीय उपयोग ; इस वायुयान, उतावले the पवित्र गाय, transported अध्यक्ष Franklin D. रूज़वेल्ट to the Yalta Conference in फ़रवरी 1945, and was subsequently प्रयुक्त लिये another two years by अध्यक्ष Harry S. Truman.
The `` एयर Force एक '' call चिह्न थी निर्मित बाद a 1953 घटना during which a flight carrying अध्यक्ष Dwight D. आइज़नहावर डाला the वही airspace as a वाणिज्यिक एयरलाइन उड़ान using the वही कॉल चिह्न.
अनेक aircraft have been प्रयुक्त as एयर Force One चूंकि the creation of the अध्यक्षीय fleet, including दो Boeing 707s introduced in the 1960s और 1970s, respectively ; चूंकि 1990, the presidential बेड़े रै consisted of two Boeing VC-25As – specifically विन्यस्त, अत्यधिक customized बोइंग 747-200B श्रेणी aircraft.
the एयर फ़ोर्स is looking into replacing the two vc-25 aircraft साथ तीन replacement वायुयान beginning in 2017.
a विवाह वर्षगांठ is the anniversary of the तिथि a विवाह took प्लेस.
परंपरागत names मौजूद लिये most of उन्हें : लिये उदाहरण, 50 years of विवाह is पुकारा a `` सुनहरी विवाह वर्षगांठ '' or बस a `` सुनहरी वर्षगांठ ''.
a स्कैनर with duplexing स्वचालित Document Feeder.
In multifunction or all-in-one मुद्रक, फैक्स machines, photocopiers और scanners, an स्वचालित दस्तावेज़ feeder or adf is a feature जिससे takes अनेक पृष्ठों और फ़ीड्स the paper one पेज at a time into a scanner or copier, allowing the उपयोक्ता to स्कैन, और thereby नक़ल, छपाई, or फैक्स, multiple-page documents without having to हस्तचालित बदलें each पेज.
सबसे copiers allow स्कैनिंग on the फ्लैटबेड or platen ( the `` कांच '' ) or through a दस्तावेज़ फीडर.
the vast majority of fax मशीने have an ADF, allowing the unattended sending of multi-page faxes.
due to the ubiquity of ADF in फैक्स मशीने, कुछ फैक्स यंत्र स्वामी उपयोग the fax machine as a स्कैनर, faxing multi-page दस्तावेज़ to themselves.
दस्तावेज़ feeders हैं वर्णित by गति, in pages प्रति मिनट or ppm, और क्षमता, usually in a दायरा इससे 10 चादरें to 200.
वहीँ are two kinds of document feeders सक्षम of two-sided ( duplex ) scanning : a reversing स्वचालित document feeder or RADF scans one side of a पेज, तब flips it और scans the other पक्ष.
a duplexing automatic दस्तावेज़ फीडर or dadf scans दोनो sides in एक pass.
The लाभ of the dadf is तेज़ गति लिये two-sided मूल.
radfs और dadfs are रेटेड in बिंब प्रति मिनट ( ipm ), the number of पहलू वे can स्कैन प्रत्येक मिनट.
मेला पार्क is a recreational and शैक्षणिक complex located in डलास, टेक्सास ( USA ).
the जटिल is registered as a डलास लैंडमार्क, National Historic लैंडमार्क और is home to नौ संग्रहालय, six performance facilities, a लैगून, and the largest फेरिस व्हील in उत्तर अमेरिका.
अनेक of the इमारतें on the जटिल यहूद constructed for the टेक्सास centennial Exposition in 1936 which खींचा over six million विज़िटर.
सबसे of the इमारतें निर्मित लिये the exposition स्टिल जीवित and it is recognized as a significant example of आर्ट डेको architecture.
मेला Park रै महरूम designated a ग्रेट प्लेस in America by the American नियोजन Association.
The American नियोजन Association ( apa ) “is an स्वतंत्र, not-for-profit educational संगठन that provides leadership in the development of vital communities.”
the Great स्थान in American program helps to celebrate क्षेत्रों साथ “exemplary अक्षर, quality, and planning.”
होने designated as a Great Place in अमेरिका, Fair पार्क थी एक of तभी टेन cities चुनी in 2011.
सैन Jose ( ; स्पेनी : st. जोसेफ ) is the third-largest नगर in कैलिफ़ोर्निया, the tenth-largest in the u.S., और the county seat of सांता क्लारा काउंटी जिससे is स्तिथ at the southern end of सैन Francisco खाड़ी.
सैन जोस is the largest नगर भीतर सिलिकॉन घाटी, जिससे is a प्रमुख घटक of the वृहद San फ्रांसिस्को खाड़ी Area, a प्रदेश of 8.4 लाख लोगों and the fifth largest महानगर क्षेत्रफल ( CSA ) in the संयुक्त राज्य.
it is the largest नगर in Northern कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
सैन जोस was संस्थापित on November 29, 1777, as El Pueblo de सैन जोस de Guadalupe, the पहला civilian कस्बा in the Spanish colony of नुएवा कैलिफ़ोर्निया, जिससे later became alta कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
The city परोसा as a farming जातियाँ to support स्पेनी military installations at San Francisco और Monterey.
जब कैलिफ़ोर्निया gained statehood in 1850, सैन जोस परोसा as इसके पहला पूंजी.
After more than 150 सालो as a छोटी खेती नगर, San Jose और the surrounding Santa Clara घाटी became the पिछला ( और largest ) contiguous क्षेत्रफल of undeveloped land surrounding the San फ्रांसिस्को खाड़ी.
San जोस experienced increased demand लिये housing इससे soldiers और दिग्गजों returning from संसार War ii.
सैन जोस then जारी its aggressive विस्तार दौरान the 1950s और 1960s by annexing more जमीन area.
the रैपिड विकास of the high-technology और electronics industries further त्वरित the परिवर्तन इससे an agricultural center, to an urbanized महानगर area.
by the 1990s, San जोस 's स्थान within the booming local प्रौद्योगिकी उद्योग अर्जित the नगर इसके nickname, पूंजी of सिलिकॉन घाटी.
सैन जोस अभी maintains global नगर औकात and is the largest नगर in the सैन फ्रांसिस्को खाड़ी क्षेत्रफल in शर्तें of population, जमीन क्षेत्रफल, और औद्योगिक विकास.
The u.S. जनसांख्यिकी ब्यूरो reported the population of the नगर to be 945,942 as of the 2010 Census.
As of अप्रैल 2013, the estimated population of San जोस was 984,000.
सैन Jose, along with the सांता Clara Valley, अनुभवी about हाफ a century of spectacular suburban sprawl, साथ विशेषताएँ of intense शहरी समान to the Los एंजिल्स क्षेत्रफल of Southern कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
The नगर has लिया definite कदम to avoid बनने `` L.A. उत्तर ''.
However, the sprawl in सैन Jose is worse than in लॉस एंजिल्स by उपायों such as जनसांख्यिकी घनत्व and public पारगमन safety, investment, और ridership.
यूरोपीय depicted by antwerp cartographer अब्राहम Ortelius in 1595
the history of यूरोपीय कवर the people inhabiting the यूरोपीय महाद्वीप since it थी पहला आबादी in प्रागैतिहासिक टाइम्स to present, साथ the पहला होमो sapiens arriving between 45,000 और 25,000 BC.
the earliest settlers to Prehistoric Europe आए दौरान the paleolithic era.
The arrival of agriculture around 7000 BC ushered in the पाषाणकालीन आयु.
Neolithic यूरोपीय lasted लिये 4000 सालो, overlapping with metal-using cultures कि धीरे स्प्रेड throughout the महाद्वीप.
technological अग्रिम during the prehistoric आयु tended to arrive इससे the मध्य ईस्ट, spreading धीरे to the उत्तरपश्चिम.
कुछ of the best-known civilizations of प्रागैतिहासिक Europe were मिनोआई और Mycenaean, which flourished दौरान the कांस्य आयु until वे collapsed in a छोटी काल of time around 1200 bc.
the काल known as classical प्राचीनता began साथ the rise of the city-states of प्राचीन यूनानियों.
Greek influence पहुँचे इसके zenith अंतर्गत the expansive साम्राज्य of Alexander the ग्रेट, spreading throughout Asia.
Northern और पश्चिमी Europe यहूद वर्चस्व by the La Tène संस्कृति, a precursor to the celts.
रोम, a small city-state traditionally संस्थापित in 753 bc, होता grow to become the रोमन गणतंत्र in 509 BC and होता succeed यूनानी culture as the dominant भूमध्यसागरीय civilization.
the कार्यक्रम of the नियम of जूलियस सीज़र led to reorganization of the गणतंत्र into the रोमन Empire.
the साम्राज्य थी बाद divided by the सम्राट diocletian into the Western and Eastern empires.
दौरान the later सालो of the रोमन साम्राज्य, the germanic peoples of उत्तरी Europe grew in शक्ति और repeated हमले led to the पतन of the पश्चिमी Roman Empire in ad 476, a date which traditionally marks the समाप्त of the classical period और the प्रारंभ of the मध्य Ages.
दौरान the मध्य आयु, the पूर्वी रोमन साम्राज्य survived, though modern historians refer to इस राज्य as the बीज़ान्टिन साम्राज्य.
in Western यूरोपीय, Germanic peoples स्थानांतरित into स्थितियाँ of शक्ति in the remnants of the former Western Roman साम्राज्य and established kingdoms और empires of उनके अपना.
of सब of the Germanic peoples, the franks होता वृद्धि to a position of आधिपत्य over western Europe, the frankish साम्राज्य reaching इसके peak अंतर्गत शारलेमेन around ad 800.

कलाकार 's धारणा of a आदिग्रह डिस्क
the गठन and of the सौर प्रणाली is अनुमानित to have begun 4.6 billion सालो ago with the गुरुत्वाकर्षक पतन of a छोटी part of a दानव molecular बादल.
Most of the collapsing द्रव्यमान collected in the केन्द्र, forming the Sun, जबकि the rest flattened into a आदिग्रह disk आउट of जिससे the ग्रह, moons, asteroids, और अन्य छोटी सौर प्रणाली लाशें formed.
इस widely स्वीकृत मॉडल, known as the nebular परिकल्पना, was पहला developed in the 18th century by emanuel Swedenborg, immanuel kant, and Pierre-Simon Laplace.
इसके subsequent विकास has interwoven a variety of वैज्ञानिक disciplines सहित astronomy, भौतिकी, geology, और planetary विज्ञान.
Since the भोर of the स्पेस आयु in the 1950s and the discovery of extrasolar planets in the 1990s, the मॉडल has been both challenged और refined to खाता लिये नई observations.
the सौर System रै evolved considerably चूंकि its आरंभिक गठन.
Many moons have formed इससे circling discs of gas और dust around उनके parent planets, जबकि अन्य moons are thought to have formed independently और बाद महरूम captured by उनके planets.
Still अन्य, as the Earth 's चंद्रमा, may be the result of giant टक्करों.
Collisions between bodies have occurred continually up to the present दिन और have been सेंट्रल to the एवोल्यूशन of the सौर System.
the स्थितियाँ of the ग्रह प्रायः shifted, और ग्रह have switched places.
इस ग्रहीय माइग्रेशन is अभी विचार to have महरूम responsible लिये much of the सौर प्रणाली 's जल्दी एवोल्यूशन.
In roughly 5 अरब सालो, the सूर्य होगा cool and expand outward many टाइम्स इसके वर्तमान व्यास ( becoming a रेड दानव ), before ढलाई off इसके बाहरी परतों as a ग्रहीय नीहारिका and leaving behind a तारकीय remnant known as a श्वेत बौना.
in the far distant भविष्य, the gravity of passing सितारों होगा धीरे reduce the सूर्य 's retinue of ग्रह.
कुछ planets will be नष्ट, others ejected into अंतरतारकीय स्पेस.
ultimately, over the course of tens of billions of years, it is likely that the Sun होगा be बाएँ with none of the असली bodies in orbit around it.
The Trial ( Kafka 's original जर्मनी title :, बाद as, and ) is a अनोखा लिखा by फ्रांज Kafka in 1914 और 1915 but नहीं प्रकाशित जबतक 1925.
One of काफ्का 's best-known works, it tells the स्टोरी of a man arrested and prosecuted by a remote, अभिगम्य authority, with the प्रकृति of his अपराधों नाज़िल to neither him nor the रीडर.

Because of this there are निश्चित inconsistencies जिससे मौजूद भीतर the novel, ऐसे as असमानताओं in समय in addition to other discontinuities in narration.

the मादा आंकड़े स्वतंत्रता और ceres, प्रतिनिधि of the state 's motto ( देखिए अगला मद ).
Liberty is holding a स्टाफ supporting a `` स्वतंत्रता cap `` ; Ceres is holding an overflowing cornucopia.
the streamer at the foot of the emblem contains the राज्य Motto of नई Jersey, `` स्वतंत्रता और Prosperity '', और the साल of statehood, 1776.
It थी originally designed by Pierre यूजीन du Simitiere in 1777 and थी modified slightly in 1928.
The seal is the central मोटिफ in the flag of New Jersey और the ग्रेट Seal of the State of New जर्सी.

the दो देवियाँ represent the राज्य motto, `` Liberty और समृद्धि ''.
Liberty is on the बाएँ.
वो is पकड़कर a स्टाफ with a स्वतंत्रता कैप on it, and the word liberty underneath उसके.

According to the मिनट्स of the New जर्सी सामान्य Assembly लिये March 11, 1896, the date in जिससे the सभा officially approved the ध्वज as the राज्य emblem, the buff रंग is due indirectly to George वॉशिंगटन, who था ordered on अक्तूबर 2, 1779, that the uniform coats of the नई Jersey महाद्वीपीय Line be अंधेरा ( जर्सी ) ब्लू, with buff facings.

As a चिकित्सा निदान, pedophilia or paedophilia is a psychiatric विकार in persons 16 years of आयु or older typically characterized by a प्राथमिक or विशेष यौन ब्याज toward prepubescent children ( generally आयु 11 सालो or younger, हालांकि विशिष्ट diagnosis criteria लिये the विकार extends the cut-off point for prepubescence to age 13 ).
an adolescent जो is 16 years of age or older must be at least पाँच सालो पुरानी than the prepubescent चाइल्ड पहले the आकर्षण can be diagnosed as pedophilia.
The term has a दायरा of definitions, as मिला in psychiatry, मनोविज्ञान, the देशी, और विधि प्रवर्तन.
the अंतरराष्ट्रीय वर्गीकरण of रोगों ( ICD ) defines pedophilia as a `` विकार of वयस्क व्यक्तित्व और behaviour '' in जिससे वहीँ is a यौन वरीयता लिये children of prepubertal or जल्दी pubertal आयु.
according to the Diagnostic and Statistical हस्तचालित of दिमागी Disorders ( DSM ), it is a paraphilia in जिससे वयस्कों or adolescents 16 सालो of age or पुरानी have तीव्र और तूल यौन प्रेरणाएं towards and कल्पनाओं परिचय prepubescent children that वे have either acted on or जिससे cause उन्हें तकलीफ or interpersonal परेशानी.
in लोकप्रिय उपयोग, pedophilia means कोई sexual ब्याज in children or the act of चाइल्ड यौन गाली, often termed `` pedophilic behavior ''.
For example, the American विरासत Stedman 's Medical शब्दकोष states, `` Pedophilia is the act or काल्पनिक on the भाग of an वयस्क of engaging in sexual activity with a child or children. ''
This common use अनुप्रयोग also extends to the sexual ब्याज in और यौन contact साथ रोमिल or post-pubescent नाबालिग.
Researchers recommend that ये imprecise uses be avoided क्युकी हालांकि people जो कमिट चाइल्ड sexual गाली commonly प्रदर्शनी the disorder, कुछ अपराधियों do not मिलें the clinical निदान मानकों लिये pedophilia और ये मानकों pertain to prepubescents.
additionally, not सब pedophiles दरअसल कमिट such गाली.
Pedophilia थी पहला formally पहचाना और नामित in the लेट 19th सदी.
a significant amount of शोध in the क्षेत्रफल रै taken प्लेस चूंकि the 1980s.
हालांकि ज़्यादातर प्रलेखित in men, there are भी महिलाओं जो प्रदर्शनी the विकार, and researchers assume उपलब्धियाँ estimates underrepresent the true क्रमांक of female pedophiles.
no cure लिये pedophilia has been developed, but there are therapies कि can reduce the incidence of a person committing child यौन abuse.
In the संयुक्त राज्य, following Kansas v. hendricks, sex अपराधियों जो हैं diagnosed साथ निश्चित दिमागी disorders, particularly pedophilia, can be विषय to indefinite civil प्रतिबद्धता, अंतर्गत various state कानून ( generically called svp कानून ) and the संघीय आदम Walsh Child Protection और सुरक्षा Act of 2006.
at उपस्थित, the सटीक causes of pedophilia have not been conclusively स्थापित.
Research suggests that pedophilia may be correlated with अनेक अलग neurological abnormalities, और often co-exists साथ अन्य व्यक्तित्व disorders और psychological pathologies.
in the contexts of forensic मनोविज्ञान and law प्रवर्तन, a किस्में of typologies have been सुझाया to categorize pedophiles according to behavior और motivations.
जूलियो césar chávez ( born Julio César chávez gonzález on जुलाई 12, 1962 ) is a रिटायर्ड Mexican पेशेवर boxer.
chávez is considered by अनेक people for उनके खेल आंकडे the महानतम fighter ever to come out of मैक्सिको.
He is a six-time संसार चैंपियन in तीन weight divisions, and for several सालो he थी माना एक of the बेहतरीन pound-for-pound boxer in the संसार.
In a career that spanned over 25 years, Chávez जीती पाँच world titles in तीन वज़न विभाजन : wbc Super featherweight in 1984, WBA lightweight in 1987, wbc lightweight in 1988, WBC लाइट welterweight in 1989, ibf लाइट Welterweight in 1990, और wbc Light welterweight in 1994.
he holds records लिये सबसे successful लगातार defenses of world शीर्षक ( 27 ), सबसे title fights ( 37 ), सबसे title-fight victories ( 31 ) और he is after जो Louis with ( 23 ) लिये सबसे शीर्षक defenses won by knockout ( 21 ).

The holocaust ( from the यूनानी ' : hólos, `` whole '' and kaustós, `` burnt '' ) भी known as the Shoah ( यहूदी :, hashoah, `` catastrophe '' ; Yiddish :, Churben or hurban, इससे the Hebrew लिये `` destruction '' ), was the द्रव्यमान हत्या or genocide of approximately छह million यहूदियों during संसार युद्ध II, a कार्यक्रम of व्यवस्थित state-sponsored हत्या by Nazi जर्मनी, led by Adolf Hitler और the Nazi Party, throughout German-occupied territory.
Of the नौ लाख Jews जो था resided in यूरोपीय पहले the Holocaust, approximately two-thirds were मारे.
Over एक million Jewish children were killed in the holocaust, as यहूद लगभग दो लाख यहूदी women and three लाख यहूदी men.
A network of over 40,000 सुविधाएं in जर्मनी and German-occupied territory यहूद प्रयुक्त to concentrate, hold, और kill यहूदियों और other victims.
कुछ scholars argue कि the mass हत्या of the romani and लोगों साथ disabilities चाहिए be शामिल in the परिभाषा, and कुछ use the common noun `` holocaust '' to describe other Nazi mass murders, सहित those of Soviet prisoners of युद्ध, पॉलिश और सोवियत civilians, and homosexuals.
Recent estimates based on आंकड़े obtained since the पतन of the सोवियत Union indicates some टेन to eleven लाख civilians और prisoners of war were intentionally murdered by the Nazi regime.
the persecution और नरसंहार यहूद carried आउट in चरण.
विभिन्न laws to remove the यहूदियों इससे सिविल society, most prominently the nuremberg Laws, यहूद enacted in Germany सालो पहले the outbreak of World युद्ध II.
Concentration camps were established in which inmates were वशीभूत to स्लेव मजदूर जबतक they died of थकावट or disease.
Where Germany conquered new territory in पूर्वी यूरोपीय, specialized इकाई पुकारा Einsatzgruppen murdered यहूदियों और political प्रतिद्वंद्वियों in mass shootings.
the occupiers जरूरी यहूदियों और Romani to be confined in overcrowded ghettos पहले being transported by freight train to extermination camps जहाँ, if वे survived the यात्रा, सबसे यहूद systematically मारे in गैस कक्षों.
प्रत्येक भुजा of Germany 's bureaucracy थी शामिल in the लोजिस्टिक्स कि led to the genocides, turning the Third reich into what एक holocaust scholar has called `` a genocidal state ''.
4-h in the संयुक्त राज्य is a youth organization administered by the नेशनल संस्थान of खाना और कृषि of the संयुक्त States विभाग of कृषि ( USDA ), साथ the मिशन of `` engaging youth to reach their fullest संभावित जबकि advancing the field of युवावस्था development. ''
the name represents four निजी विकास क्षेत्रों of focus लिये the organization : head, heart, hands, और health.
the organization रै over 6.5 लाख सदस्यों in the संयुक्त States, इससे आयु पाँच to twenty-one, in approximately 90,000 clubs.
The लक्ष्य of 4-H is to develop नागरिकता, नेतृत्व, जिम्मेदारी और life कौशल of युवावस्था through experiential learning कार्यक्रम and a positive युवावस्था विकास approach.
Though typically thought of as an agriculturally केन्द्रित organization as a परिणाम of इसके इतिहास, 4-h आज focuses on citizenship, healthy जीना, science, अभियान्त्रिकी, and technology programs.
आज, 4-h और related कार्यक्रम मौजूद in over eighty देशों around the संसार ; the organization and प्रशासन varies इससे country to देश.
Each of ये programs operates independently, but cooperatively through international exchanges, global शिक्षा programs, और communications.
The 4-H motto is `` to make the बेहतरीन better '', जबकि इसके स्लोगन is `` सीख by doing '' ( sometimes लिखा as `` सीख to do by doing '' ).

Virginia ( ), officially the राष्ट्रमंडल of वर्जिनिया, is a u.S. राज्य located in the दक्षिण अटलांटिक region of the संयुक्त States.
वर्जिनिया is nicknamed the `` Old Dominion '' और the `` माँ of राष्ट्रपतियों '' बाद the आठ U.S. presidents born वहीँ.
the भूगोल and जलवायु of the राष्ट्रमंडल हैं तराशा by the Blue लकीरें Mountains और the Chesapeake Bay, जिससे provide आवास for much of इसके फ्लोरा और fauna.
The capital of the राष्ट्रमंडल is Richmond ; और वर्जिनिया बीच is the most populous नगर.
फेयरफैक्स काउंटी is the सबसे populous political subdivision.
the wealthiest is loudoun काउंटी.
the Commonwealth 's जनसांख्यिकी is over eight लाख.
The क्षेत्रफल 's history begins with several स्वदेशी समूह, सहित the Powhatan.
In 1607 the लंदन कम्पनी established the Colony of Virginia as the first स्थाई New World अंग्रेज़ी colony.
स्लेव मजदूर and the land acquired from displaced देशी अमरीकी tribes each निभाई a significant भूमिका in the colony 's early राजनीती और वृक्षारोपण अर्थव्यवस्था.
Virginia थी one of the 13 Colonies in the American क्रान्ति और joined the Confederacy in the American सिविल युद्ध, दौरान जिससे Richmond थी बना the Confederate पूंजी और Virginia 's northwestern counties seceded to रूप the state of West वर्जिनिया.
हालांकि the राष्ट्रमंडल was अंतर्गत रूढ़िवादी single-party नियम लिये nearly a सदी following पुनर्निर्माण, दोनो major नेशनल पार्टियों हैं competitive in आधुनिक वर्जिनिया.
the वर्जिनिया General सभा is the oldest विधानमंडल in the पश्चिमी Hemisphere.
The राज्य सरकारी has महरूम repeatedly क्रमित most effective by the pew बीच on the राज्य.
It is unique in how it treats cities and काउंटी equally, manages लोकल सड़कें, और prohibits इसके governors इससे serving लगातार terms.
वर्जिनिया 's अर्थव्यवस्था रै many सेक्टर : कृषि in the shenandoah घाटी ; संघीय एजेंसियों in Northern Virginia, सहित the मुख्यालय of the विभाग of रक्षा और सीआईए ; और military facilities in Hampton सड़कें, the साईट of the region 's प्रमुख seaport.
वर्जिनिया 's पब्लिक स्कूलों and अनेक colleges and universities have contributed to growing media और technology sectors.
As a result, कंप्यूटर chips have become the राज्य 's leading export.

in नवम्बर 2005, 4Kids Entertainment, जिससे था प्रबंधित the non-game सम्बन्धित लाइसेंसिंग of पोकीमॉन, घोषित कि it था सहमत नहीं to renew the पोकीमॉन प्रतिनिधित्व अनुबंध.

The पद पोकीमॉन, in जोड to referring to the Pokémon franchise itself, भी collectively refers to the 649 fictional species that have बना appearances in पोकीमॉन मीडिया as of the रिलीज of the पांचवां पीढी शीर्षक Pokémon Black 2 and White 2 ; साथ the आगामी रिलीज of पोकीमॉन x और Y, 6 new Pokémon have been प्रदर्शित in प्रचार लिये the games.
`` Pokémon '' is identical in दोनो the singular और बहुवचन, as is each individual species नाम ; it is grammatically सही to say `` एक पोकीमॉन '' और `` अनेक Pokémon '', as खूब as `` एक Pikachu `` और `` अनेक Pikachu ''.

Dada ( ) or Dadaism थी an आर्ट movement of the European avant-garde in the जल्दी 20th सदी.
Many claim दादा began in ज्यूरिख, स्विट्ज़रलैंड in 1916, spreading to Berlin shortly thereafter लकिन the height of नई York Dada was the year पहले in 1915.
to quote डोना Budd 's the भाषा of Art ज्ञान, Dada was born आउट of negative reaction to the horrors of संसार War I.
इस international गति थी begun by a समूह of artist और कवियों associated with the कैबरे Voltaire in Zurich.
Dada rejected कारण और लॉजिक, prizing बकवास, irrationality और अंतर्ज्ञान.
The उत्पत्ति of the name Dada is unclear ; कुछ believe that it is a nonsensical word.
अन्य maintain कि it originates from the रोमानियाई artists Tristan Tzara और मार्सल janco 's frequent उपयोग of the शब्द da, da, अर्थ यस, yes in the रोमानियाई language.
another सिद्धान्त says that the name `` Dada '' came दौरान a meeting of the समूह when a paper चाकू stuck into a french-german dictionary happened to पाइंट to 'डैडa ', a फ्रेंच word लिये 'hobbyhorse '.
the गति primarily involved visual कला, साहित्य, काव्य, art manifestoes, art सिद्धान्त, theatre, और graphic design, और concentrated इसके anti-war राजनीती through a rejection of the प्रचलित मानकों in आर्ट through anti-art सांस्कृतिक works.
In जोड to being anti-war, दादा was भी anti- बुर्जुआ and had राजनैतिक affinities साथ the कट्टरपंथी left.
दादा क्रियाएँ शामिल पब्लिक महफिलों, demonstrations, और प्रकाशन of art/literary जर्नल्स ; passionate कवरेज of आर्ट, राजनीती, and संस्कृति यहूद topics प्रायः discussed in a किस्में of media.
Key आंकड़े in the गति शामिल Hugo Ball, Emmy hennings, hans arp, raoul hausmann, Hannah höch, योहानेस baader, ट्रिस्टन tzara, फ्रांसिस picabia, Richard huelsenbeck, georg grosz, जॉन heartfield, Marcel Duchamp, Beatrice Wood, Kurt schwitters, and hans Richter, among अन्य.
The गति बहकावे बाद styles जैसे the avant-garde और downtown music movements, और समूह including surrealism, Nouveau réalisme, पॉप आर्ट और Fluxus.
दादा is the groundwork to अमूर्त आर्ट और sound काव्य, a starting पाइंट for performance आर्ट, a prelude to postmodernism, an influence on पॉप art, a celebration of antiart to be later embraced for anarcho-political uses in the 1960s और the movement कि lay the न्यास for Surrealism.
पहला trophic level.
The plants in इस image, और the algae and phytoplankton in the lake, हैं प्राथमिक निर्माता.
वे take nutrients इससे the soil or the water, और manufacture उनके अपना food by photosynthesis, using energy from the sun.
The trophic level of an सजीव is the position it occupies in a खाना कड़ी.
the word trophic गर्भाशयी इससे the यूनानी τροφή ( trophē ) referring to food or feeding.
A खाना कड़ी represents a उत्तराधिकार of जीवों कि खा another सजीव and are, in turn, खाया themselves.
the number of कदम an सजीव is इससे the start of the कड़ी is a माप of its trophic स्तर.
खाना जंजीरों प्रारंभ at trophic स्तर 1 साथ प्राथमिक producers such as पौधे, move to herbivores at स्तर 2, परभक्षी at स्तर 3 and typically समाप्त साथ carnivores or apex predators at स्तर 4 or 5.
The पाथ साथ the कड़ी can form either a one-way प्रवाह, or a food `` वेब. ''
Ecological communities साथ उच्चतर biodiversity रूप अधिक complex trophic राहें.
Four of the सबसे important domesticated silk moths.
Top to नीचे : Bombyx mori, hyalophora cecropia, antheraea pernyi, samia सिंथिया.

A silk-producing raspy क्रिकेट.
रेशा is a natural प्रोटीन fibre, कुछ फ़ॉर्म of which can be woven into textiles.
the protein fibre of रेशा is रचित mainly of fibroin और produced by निश्चित कीट larvae to form cocoons.
the best-known type of silk is प्राप्त इससे the cocoons of the larvae of the शहतूत silkworm Bombyx mori reared in captivity ( sericulture ).
the shimmering रूप of रेशा is due to the triangular प्रिज़्म -like structure of the रेशा fibre, which allows silk cloth to refract आवक लाइट at अलग angles, यूँ producing different colors.
silks are produced by several other कीट, लकिन generally only the रेशा of moth caterpillars रै been प्रयुक्त for textile निर्माण.
There रै महरूम कुछ शोध into अन्य silks, जिससे differ at the molecular स्तर.
अनेक silks हैं mainly produced by the larvae of कीट undergoing पूरा metamorphosis, but कुछ वयस्क कीट ऐसे as webspinners उपज रेशा, और कुछ insects ऐसे as raspy झींगुर उपज रेशा throughout उनके जीवनदान.
Silk उत्पादन भी occurs in कलापक्ष ( मधुमक्खियों, wasps, और ants ), silverfish, mayflies, thrips, leafhoppers, भृंग, lacewings, fleas, उड़ता और midges.
अन्य प्रकार of सन्धिपाद produce रेशा, सबसे notably विभिन्न arachnids ऐसे as spiders ( see मकड़ी silk ).

cyberstalking is the use of the Internet or अन्य इलेक्ट्रॉनिक means to stalk or harass an individual, a group of individuals, or an organization.
it may include the making of गलत accusations or statements of fact ( as in मानहानि ), निगरानी, बनाना खतरे, पहचान चोरी, damage to आंकड़ा or equipment, the solicitation of नाबालिग लिये sex, or gathering information कि may be प्रयुक्त to harass.
the परिभाषा of `` उत्पीड़न '' must मिलें the मानदंड कि a reasonable व्यक्ति, in कब्ज़ा of the वही सूचना, would regard it as sufficient to कारण another उचित person तकलीफ.

however, it sometimes लीड to it, or is accompanied by it.
Both हैं दण्ड offenses.
Cyberstalking shares महत्वपूर्ण विशेषताएँ साथ ऑफ़लाइन stalking.
अनेक stalkers – ऑनलाइन or बंद – are motivated by a desire to कंट्रोल their victims.
a cyberstalker may be an ऑनलाइन stranger or a person जिसको the निशाना knows.
A cyberstalker may be बेनाम और may solicit involvement of other people online जो do नहीं even know the निशाना.

a cyberstalking conviction can परिणाम in a restraining order, probation, or भी दण्ड penalties विरूद्ध the assailant, सहित कारावास.

एडोल्फ Hitler ( ; 20 April 1889 – 30 April 1945 ) थी an आस्ट्रिया -born German राजनेता and the नेता of the नाजी पार्टी ( ( nsdap ) ; National समाजवादी German मजदूर Party ).
he was chancellor of Germany from 1933 to 1945 and तानाशाह of Nazi जर्मनी ( as Führer und Reichskanzler ) इससे 1934 to 1945.
हिटलर थी at the centre of नाजी Germany, संसार War ii in यूरोपीय, and the Holocaust.
Hitler थी a decorated veteran of संसार युद्ध i.
He joined the जर्मनी मजदूर ' Party ( precursor of the NSDAP ) in 1919, और became नेता of the nsdap in 1921.
In 1923, he attempted a coup d'état in म्यूनिख, known as the Beer हॉल putsch.
The failed तख्तापलट resulted in हिटलर 's imprisonment, दौरान जिससे time he wrote his संस्मरण, Mein Kampf ( my संघर्ष ).
बाद his रिलीज in 1924, Hitler gained लोकप्रिय support by attacking the Treaty of versailles and promoting Pan-Germanism, antisemitism, और anti-communism with charismatic oratory और Nazi प्रचार.
बाद his appointment as चांसलर in 1933, he transformed the Weimar गणतंत्र into the तीसरा reich, a single-party तानाशाही आधारित on the अधिनायकवादी और निरंकुश विचारधारा of Nazism.
Hitler 's उद्देश्य थी to establish a New Order of निरपेक्ष Nazi जर्मनी hegemony in continental Europe.
to इस समाप्त, उसके foreign और domestic नीतियों had the aim of seizing Lebensraum ( `` living space '' ) लिये the germanic लोगों.
he directed the rearmament of Germany और the आक्रमण of Poland by the wehrmacht in सितंबर 1939, resulting in the outbreak of संसार युद्ध II in यूरोपीय.
Under Hitler 's नियम, in 1941 जर्मनी शक्तियां and their European allies occupied सबसे of Europe और उत्तर Africa.
in 1943, जर्मनी था महरूम मजबूर onto the रक्षात्मक and suffered a श्रेणी of escalating defeats.
in the फाइनल दिनों of the युद्ध, दौरान the बैटल of Berlin in 1945, हिटलर शादीशुदा his long-time संगी, एवा braun.
On 30 April 1945, कम than two days बाद, the दो committed आत्महत्या to avoid कैप्चर by the रेड Army, और उनके शवों were burned.
Hitler 's आक्रामक विदेशी नीति is माना the प्रमुख कारण of the outbreak of World War II in यूरोपीय.
His antisemitic नीतियों and racially प्रेरित विचारधारा resulted in the deaths of at least 5.5 million Jews, and लाखो of other लोगों deemed racially अवर.

A domain नाम is an पहचान स्ट्रिंग कि defines a realm of administrative autonomy, प्राधिकार, or control on the अंतरजाल.
Domain names हैं formed by the नियम and procedures of the डोमेन Name प्रणाली ( DNS ).
technically, any नाम registered in the डीएनएस is a डोमेन name.
डोमेन names are प्रयुक्त in विभिन्न नेटवर्किंग contexts and application-specific naming और संबोधित उद्देश्य.
In सामान्य, a डोमेन नाम represents an अंतरजाल प्रोटोकॉल ( IP ) संसाधन, ऐसे as a निजी कंप्यूटर प्रयुक्त to अभिगम the अंतरजाल, a server computer होस्टिंग a वेब साईट, or the web साईट itself or any other service communicated via the अंतरजाल.
Domain names are व्यवस्थित in अधीनस्थ levels ( subdomains ) of the DNS रूट डोमेन, जिससे is nameless.
the first-level नियत of डोमेन names हैं the top-level domains ( tlds ), including the generic top-level domains ( gtlds ), such as the prominent domains com, सूचना, जाल और org, और the country कोड top-level डोमेन ( cctlds ).
नीचे these top-level domains in the डीएनएस पदानुक्रम हैं the second-level और third-level domain names that हैं typically खोलें लिये reservation by end-users who काश to connect लोकल क्षेत्रफल संजाल to the अंतरजाल, बनाएँ अन्य सरेआम accessible Internet resources or run web sites.
the पंजीकरण of ये डोमेन names is usually administered by डोमेन नाम registrars who बेचें their सेवाएं to the public.
a fully योग्य domain name ( FQDN ) is a डोमेन नाम that is completely निर्दिष्ट in the पदानुक्रम of the डीएनएस, having no omitted भाग.
डोमेन names हैं प्रायः लिखा in लोअरकेस, हालांकि labels in the Domain Name प्रणाली हैं case-insensitive.

The mpemba effect, नामित after tanzanian छात्र erasto mpemba, is the assertion that warmer water can freeze तेज़ than colder जल.
Although वहीँ is anecdotal support लिये the effect, वहीँ is no agreement on exactly कया the प्रभाव is और अंतर्गत what circumstances it occurs.
वहीँ have महरूम रिपोर्ट्स of समान phenomena since ancient टाइम्स, although साथ अपर्याप्त विवरण लिये the दावा to be replicated.
The घटना seems contrary to thermodynamics, लकिन a क्रमांक of possible explanations लिये the प्रभाव have महरूम प्रस्तावित.
further investigations होगा need to decide on a precise परिभाषा of `` जमने '' और control a vast number of starting पैरामीटर्स in order to confirm or explain the effect.

in अर्थशास्त्र, the money supply or money भण्डार, is the total amount of monetary एसेट उपलब्धियाँ in an economy at a specific समय.
वहीँ हैं several तरीके to define `` money, '' लकिन मानक measures प्रायः शामिल करेंसी in परिसंचरण और demand deposits ( जमाकर्ताओं ' easily पहुँचा एसेट on the किताबे of financial संस्थानों ).
Money supply आंकड़ा हैं अंकित और published, प्रायः by the सरकारी or the central bank of the देश.
पब्लिक और निजी sector analysts have long monitored changes in money supply क्युकी of इसके effects on the दाम स्तर, inflation, the एक्सचेंज रेट और the कारोबार cycle.
कि संबंध between money and कीमतें is historically संबद्ध with the मात्रा theory of धन.
वहीँ is दमदार empirical प्रमाण of a direct संबंध between money-supply विकास और long-term दाम महंगाई, at तनिक लिये रैपिड increases in the राशि of धन in the अर्थव्यवस्था.
That is, a देश such as ज़िम्बाब्वे which देखी rapid increases in इसके धन supply भी देखी rapid increases in कीमतें ( hyperinflation ).
इस is एक reason लिये the रिलायंस on मौद्रिक नीति as a अर्थात् of controlling inflation.
the प्रकृति of this causal chain is the subject of contention.
कुछ शास्त economists argue कि the धन सप्लाई is endogenous ( संकल्पित by the workings of the अर्थव्यवस्था, नहीं by the सेंट्रल बैंको ) and कि the स्त्रोत of inflation must be मिला in the distributional structure of the economy.
In addition, those अर्थशास्त्रियों देखकर the सेंट्रल bank 's कंट्रोल over the धन सप्लाई as feeble say कि वहीँ हैं two weak links between the growth of the धन सप्लाई and the महंगाई रेट.
पहला, in the aftermath of a मंदी, when many resources are underutilized, an बढ़ाएँ in the money सप्लाई can कारण a sustained बढ़ाएँ in रियल production बजाय of महंगाई.
Second, if the velocity of धन, i.e., the अनुपात between nominal GDP and धन सप्लाई, changes, an increase in the धन supply could have either no प्रभाव, an अतिरंजित प्रभाव, or an मनमौजी effect on the विकास of nominal जीडीपी.

a राजनैतिक संगठन is संवैधानिक to the extent कि it `` contain [ s ] institutionalized mechanisms of शक्ति कंट्रोल लिये the protection of the रूचि और लिबर्टीज of the citizenry, सहित those कि may be in the minority ``.
as वर्णित by राजनैतिक scientist और संवैधानिक विद्वान दाउद Fellman :
an ice-cream headache, भी known as दिमाग freeze, cold-stimulus सिरदर्द, or its दिए scientific name sphenopalatine ganglioneuralgia ( meaning `` तंत्रिका पीड़ा of the sphenopalatine गंडिका `` ), is a form of brief cranial पीड़ा or सिरदर्द commonly associated with खपत ( विशेषकर जल्दी consumption ) of ठंडा पेय or foods such as बर्फ cream and ice pops.
it is caused by having something cold टच the छत of the मुँह ( palate ), और is believed to परिणाम from a nerve जवाब causing रैपिड constriction और swelling of रक्त vessels or a `` referring `` of पीड़ा from the छत of the मुँह to the सिर.
The रेट of सेवन लिये ठंडा foods रै been studied as a contributing factor.
वहीँ हैं people जो can not experience `` दिमाग फ्रीज '' or समान लक्षण.
The term ice-cream headache has महरूम in उपयोग चूंकि at least 31 जनवरी 1937, contained in a जर्नल entry by रेबेका timbres published in the 1939 किताब we did n't ask Utopia : a quaker family in सोवियत रूस.
the first प्रकाशित उपयोग of the पद brain फ्रीज, as it pertains to cold-induced headaches, was on 27 may 1991.
`` auld लैंग syne '' ( : note `` s '' बल्कि than `` z '' ) is a स्कॉट्स poem written by Robert Burns in 1788 और set to the tune of a परंपरागत लोक सोंग ( Roud # 6294 ).
It is खूब known in अनेक countries, especially in the english-speaking संसार ; इसके परंपरागत उपयोग being to celebrate the start of the New Year at the stroke of midnight.
by एक्सटेंशन, it is भी सुंग at funerals, graduations और as a farewell or समाप्ति to other अवसरों.
the international लड़के स्काउट youth movement, in अनेक countries, उपयोग it as a बंद to jamborees और other कृत्यों.
the सोंग 's Scots शीर्षक may be अनूदित into अंग्रेज़ी literally as `` बूढ़ा long since '', or more idiomatically, `` long long ago '', `` days गए by '' or `` बूढ़ा टाइम्स ''.
नतीजतन `` For auld lang syne '', as it appears in the पहला line of the chorus, might be loosely translated as `` for ( the sake of ) old times ''.
the phrase `` auld लैंग syne '' is भी used in समान poems by Robert Ayton ( 1570–1638 ), allan Ramsay ( 1686–1757 ), और जेम्स वाटसन ( 1711 ) as खूब as पुरानी लोक गीतों predating Burns.
मैथ्यू Fitt उपयोग the phrase `` In the days of auld लैंग syne '' as the समतुल्य of `` Once upon a समय...
`` in उसके retelling of fairy tales in the Scots भाषा.

leeroy Jenkins, sometimes misspelled Leroy जेनकींस और often elongated साथ numerous अतिरिक्त अक्षर, is an अंतरजाल मीम नामित लिये a खिलाड़ी अक्षर created by बेन schulz in blizzard Entertainment 's mmorpg, संसार of warcraft.

Oscar Grant थी fatally shot by BART पुलिस officer योहानेस Mehserle in Oakland, कैलिफ़ोर्निया, संयुक्त राज्य, in the जल्दी morning घंटों of नई साल 's Day 2009.
responding to रिपोर्ट्स of a fight on a भीड़ खाड़ी Area Rapid Transit train returning इससे सैन फ्रांसिस्को, बार्ट Police अधिकारियों detained Oscar Grant और several other यात्री on the मंच at the Fruitvale BART स्टेशन.
अधिकारी Johannes mehserle and another अधिकारी यहूद restraining Grant, जो was सजदा and allegedly resisting गिरफ़्तार.
अधिकारी mehserle stood and, according to गवाह, said : `` मिलेंगी back, i 'm gon na tase उसे. ''
तब Mehserle drew उसके गन and shot Grant once in the वापस ; Mehserle appeared stunned, put his hands to उसके head and exclaimed, `` Oh, my God ! ''
दौरान उसके अदालत testimony, mehserle कहा कि ग्रान्ट then exclaimed, `` तुम शॉट me ! ''
ग्रान्ट turned आउट to be unarmed ; he was सुनाया मुर्दे the अगला morning at Highland हॉस्पिटल in ओकलैंड.
The कार्यक्रम were captured on अनेक डिजिटल video और कोशिका फोन कैमरे.
the फुटेज थी disseminated to मीडिया आउटलेट और to विभिन्न वेबसाइटों, where it थी watched लाखो of times.
the following days saw दोनो शांतिपूर्ण और violent विरोध.
The शूटिंग रै been variously labeled an involuntary manslaughter और a summary execution.
on जनवरी 13, Alameda County prosecutors चार्ज Mehserle साथ murder लिये the shooting.
He resigned his स्थिति और pleaded नहीं guilty.
The trial began on June 10, 2010.
माइकल rains, Mehserle 's criminal defense attorney, argued कि Mehserle mistakenly शॉट ग्रान्ट with उसके पिस्टल, intending to उपयोग his तासीर जब he saw ग्रान्ट reaching for उसके waistband.

Oakland civil अधिकारों attorney जॉन Burris दायर a $ 25 लाख wrongful मौत अर्जी विरूद्ध BART on behalf of ग्रान्ट 's family.
on जुलाई 8, 2010, the jury returned इसके verdict : mehserle थी found अपराधी of involuntary manslaughter और नहीं अपराधी of second-degree हत्या and voluntary manslaughter.
Initial विरोध विरूद्ध the सत्ताधारी यहूद शांतिपूर्वक व्यवस्थित ; लूटने, आगजनी, destruction of प्रॉपर्टी, and small riots broke out after dark.
nearly 80 लोगों यहूद आखिरकार गिरफ्तार.
on Friday, जुलाई 9, 2010, the u.S. इंसाफ Department खोली a civil rights मामला विरूद्ध Mehserle ; the federal सरकारी can prosecute him independently लिये the वही अधिनियम अंतर्गत the separate अधिपति एक्सेप्शन to double jeopardy.
the विभाग of इंसाफ will be working with the u.S. attorney 's office in San फ्रांसिस्को और the एफबीआई.

He परोसा his समय in the लॉस Angeles County Jail, occupying a निजी कोशिका away इससे other बंदियों.

प्रमुख प्रतिनिधि of the हार्लेम पुनर्जागरण.
The Harlem पुनर्जागरण थी a सांस्कृतिक movement कि spanned the 1920s.
at the समय, it was ज्ञात as the `` नई Negro गति '', नामित बाद the 1925 anthology by alain locke.
हालांकि it was केन्द्रित in the Harlem neighborhood of नई यॉर्क नगर, many french-speaking ब्लैक writers from African and Caribbean colonies जो जिया in Paris यहूद also influenced by the Harlem Renaissance.
the Harlem Renaissance is unofficially पहचाना to have spanned from परिचय 1919 जबतक the early or mid-1930s.
Many of इसके ideas जिया on much longer.
the zenith of इस `` flowering of नीग्रो literature '', as जेम्स weldon जॉनसन पसन्दीदा to कॉल the हार्लेम पुनर्जागरण, थी लगाई between 1924 ( the year that अवसर : A जर्नल of नीग्रो Life hosted a पार्टी लिये black writers जहाँ अनेक श्वेत publishers यहूद in उपस्थिति ) and 1929 ( the year of the भण्डार market क्रैश और the शुरूआत of the ग्रेट अवसाद ).

The इतिहास of अफ़्रीकी begins with the prehistory of Africa और the emergence of Homo sapiens in ईस्ट Africa, continuing into the उपस्थित as a patchwork of विविध and politically विकासशील स्वदेश states.
Some जल्दी evidence of agriculture in अफ़्रीकी dates from 16,000 bce, और metallurgy इससे परिचय 4000 BCE.
the recorded इतिहास of जल्दी सभ्यता arose in Egypt, और later in नुबिया, the मग़रिब और the सींग of Africa.
दौरान the Middle आयु, Islam spread through the regions.
Crossing the मग़रिब and the सहेल, a major center of मुस्लिम संस्कृति थी Timbuktu.
Some notable pre-colonial राज्य और समाजों in अफ़्रीकी शामिल the Nok culture, माली Empire, ashanti Empire, किंगडम of Mapungubwe, Kingdom of ज्या, Kingdom of saloum, किंगडम of Baol, किंगडम of ज़िम्बाब्वे, किंगडम of Kongo, प्राचीन कार्थेज, Numidia, mauretania, the Aksumite साम्राज्य, the ajuuraan राज्य and the Adal Sultanate.
From the लेट 15th सदी, Europeans और arabs took स्लेव इससे वेस्ट, सेंट्रल और southeast Africa overseas in the अफ़्रीकी स्लेव व्यापार.
यूरोपीय colonization of अफ़्रीकी विकसित rapidly in the Scramble लिये Africa of the late 19th और जल्दी 20th centuries.
following struggles for स्वतंत्रता in अनेक भाग of the महाद्वीप, as well as a weakened यूरोपीय बाद the Second World War ; decolonization took प्लेस.
Africa 's इतिहास has been चुनौतीपूर्ण लिये शोधकर्ताओं in the फ़ील्ड of African studies क्युकी of the किल्लत of written sources in large भाग of sub-Saharan अफ़्रीकी.
Scholarly techniques such as the रिकॉर्डिंग of मौखिक इतिहास, ऐतिहासिक भाषाविज्ञान, पुरातत्व and आनुवंशिकी have महरूम crucial.
Curry फोली थी the first खिलाड़ी in Major लीग Baseball इतिहास to hit लिये the cycle.
In baseball, hitting लिये the साईकिल is the accomplishment of एक batter hitting a सिंगल, a दोगुना, a ट्रिपल, और a घर run in the same game.
Collecting the हिट्स in कि order is known as a `` natural साईकिल ''.
Cycles हैं uncommon in Major लीग Baseball ( एमएलबी ), और have occurred 294 टाइम्स चूंकि the first by Curry Foley in 1882.
the cycle is roughly as common as a no-hitter ( 279 आवृत्ति in एमएलबी इतिहास ) ; it रै महरूम called `` one of the rarest '' और `` सबसे मुश्किल feats '' in baseball.
Based on 2009 अप्रिय स्तर, the संभाव्यता of an average एमएलबी खिलाड़ी hitting लिये a cycle against an औसत team in a खेल is approximately 0.00590 % ; this corresponds to परिचय 2.5 cycles in a 162-game ऋतु साथ 30 टीमों.
in अन्य baseball leagues, the साईकिल is हासिल less frequently.
through सितंबर 4, 2008, 62 players in Nippon Professional बेसबॉल ( npb ), the top-level baseball संगठन in जापानी, have hit for the cycle, the most हाल होने michihiro ogasawara.
Two खिलाड़ी have hit for the साईकिल on the same day एकबार in NPB इतिहास ; this has occurred twice in एमएलबी इतिहास.
One npb खिलाड़ी has भी hit for the साईकिल in an NPB all-star game.
No खिलाड़ी रै कभी hit लिये the cycle in the MLB all-star खेल or the postseason.
The main slave रूट in मध्यकालीन अफ़्रीकी.
This आलेख discusses प्रणालियों, इतिहास, और प्रभाव of गुलामी within Africa.
See अरब स्लेव व्यापार, अटलांटिक स्लेव व्यापार, Maafa, and गुलामी in समकालीन अफ़्रीकी for other चर्चाएँ.
`` Slave transport in अफ़्रीकी ''.
Europeans प्रायः किया नहीं डालें the interior regions.
गुलामी in Africa रै existed throughout the continent लिये अनेक सदियां, और continues in the current दिन.
प्रणालियों of servitude and slavery यहूद common in many भाग of the continent, as they were in much of the ancient world.
in most अफ़्रीकी समाजों where slavery थी प्रचलित, the enslaved people यहूद largely treated as indentured बन्दों और नहीं treated as chattel स्लेव.
When the अरब स्लेव trade and अटलांटिक slave व्यापार began, अनेक of the लोकल slave systems बदला and began supplying captives लिये slave बाज़ार outside of Africa.
गुलामी in ऐतिहासिक अफ़्रीकी थी practiced in अनेक अलग फ़ॉर्म and कुछ of these do नहीं clearly अनुरूप the definitions of slavery elsewhere in the संसार.
कर्ज़ slavery, enslavement of युद्ध captives, सैन्य slavery, and criminal गुलामी यहूद सब practiced in विभिन्न भाग of Africa.
हालांकि वहीँ था महरूम कुछ trans-Saharan trade from the interior of sub-saharan Africa to अन्य regions, slavery was a small भाग of the economic life of अनेक समाजों in अफ़्रीकी जबतक the परिचय of transcontinental स्लेव ट्रेड ( अरब and अटलांटिक ).
Slave practices यहूद again transformed साथ European colonization of अफ़्रीकी और the औपचारिक abolition of slavery in the जल्दी 1900s.

पिछला संस्करण of खिड़कियाँ NT included the कार्य List अनुप्रयोग, which था far कम features.
The कार्य list थी capable of लिस्टिंग फिलहाल running प्रक्रियाओं और हत्या उन्हें, or बनाना a नई प्रक्रम.

Sparsely आबादी in संबंध to इसके area, the लोकतांत्रिक गणतंत्र of the कांगो ( drc ) is home to a vast संभावित of प्राकृतिक resources और खनिज wealth, its untapped जमा of कच्चा खनिज हैं estimated to be लायक in excess of US $ 24 खरब, yet the अर्थव्यवस्था of the drc has declined drastically since the mid-1980s.
At the समय of इसके स्वतंत्रता in 1960, drc थी the दूसरी most industrialized देश in Africa बाद दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी ; it boasted a thriving खनन sector और इसके कृषि सेक्टर थी अपेक्षाकृत उत्पादक.
if the viewer stares at इस चित्र लिये 20–60 सेकेंड और stares at a white object, a ऋणात्मक afterimage होगा appear ( in इस मामला, it will be क्यान on magenta ).
This can also be हासिल by the viewer closing his/her eyes और tilting their सिर up.
An afterimage or ghost image or image burn-in is an ऑप्टिकल भ्रम कि refers to an चित्र continuing to appear in एक 's vision after the एक्सपोज़र to the असली चित्र has ceased.
One of the most आम afterimages is the उज्जवल glow कि seems to फ्लैश पहले एक 's eyes बाद looking into a लाइट सोर्स for a few seconds.
closing the नजर can सहायता achieve a better भाव of the रंग in its अपना पहलू.
Afterimages आइये in दो फ़ॉर्म, ऋणात्मक ( inverted ) and धनात्मक ( retaining असली रंग ).
the प्रक्रम behind positive afterimages is unknown, though विचार to be सम्बन्धित to neural अनुकूलन.
on the other हाथ, ऋणात्मक afterimages are a retinal घटना और are खूब समझा.

the श्रेणी फ़ॉलो the पास्ट, उपस्थित, and भविष्य अनुभव ( s ) of the survivors of a plane क्रैश on a passenger जेट, Oceanic Flight 815, उड़ती इससे Sydney to लॉस एंजिल्स बाद it क्रैश on a tropical द्वीप in the दक्षिण प्रशांत.

प्रत्येक एपीसोड typically सुविधाएँ action on the द्वीप as well as a secondary storyline इससे another पाइंट in a character 's life.
ऋतु 6 सुविधाएँ a detailing of the जीवनदान of the survivors in a अलग वास्तविकता, as if the उड़ान had never क्रैश.
in the following सूची, the term `` प्रदर्शित अक्षर ( s ) '' refers to the अक्षर or वर्ण जो हैं featured in the द्वितीयक कथानक of each एपीसोड.
`` No.
in series '' refers to the एपीसोड 's क्रमांक in the overall श्रेणी, whereas `` no.

Flat feet ( also called pes planus or fallen arches ) is a औपचारिक reference to a चिकित्सा condition in which the मेहराब of the foot collapses, साथ the संपूर्ण एकमात्र of the पैर coming into complete or near-complete contact साथ the ground.
in some individuals ( an अनुमानित 20–30 % of the सामान्य जनसांख्यिकी ) the मेहराब बस never develops in one foot ( unilaterally ) or दोनो फीट ( bilaterally ).
तीन studies ( देखिए citations below in सैन्य section ) of सैन्य रंगरूटों have दिखाया no प्रमाण of बाद increased चोट, or पैर problems, due to चपटा फीट, in a जनसांख्यिकी of लोगों who पहुँचें सैन्य service आयु बगैर prior पैर समस्याएं.
However, ये अध्ययन can not be used to judge संभावित future damage इससे this condition when diagnosed at younger आयु.
वे भी can not be लागू to persons जिनकी चपटा फीट are associated with foot symptoms, or certain लक्षण in other parts of the देह ( ऐसे as the लेग or वापस ) possibly referable to the foot.

Pressure छाले, भी known as decubitus ulcers or bedsores, हैं localized injuries to the स्किन and/or underlying tissue प्रायः over a bony prominence, as a result of दबाव, or pressure in combination साथ shear and/or घर्षण.
Most commonly इस होगा be the sacrum, coccyx, एड़ियों or the hips, लकिन अन्य साइट ऐसे as the elbows, knees, ankles or the वापस of the cranium can be affected.
The cause of दबाव ulcers is दबाव लागू to soft tissue so कि blood flow to the नरम tissue is completely or partially obstructed.
shear is भी a कारण ; shear खींचता on blood vessels that feed the स्किन.
दबाव छाले सबसे commonly develop in व्यक्तियों who are नहीं moving परिचय or are confined to wheelchairs.
it is widely believed कि अन्य factors can influence the सहिष्णुता of skin for दबाव and shear thereby increasing the risk of दबाव ulcer विकास.
ये factors are protein-calorie malnutrition, microclimate ( स्किन wetness caused by sweating or incontinence ), diseases कि reduce blood flow to the स्किन, ऐसे as arteriosclerosis or रोगों कि reduce the अहसास in the स्किन, such as paralysis or न्यूरोपैथी.
the healing of pressure छाले may be slowed by the आयु of the व्यक्ति, medical conditions ( ऐसे as arteriosclerosis, मधुमेह or संक्रमण ), धूम्रपान or medications such as antiinflammatory दवाएँ.
हालांकि प्रायः prevented और treatable if मिला जल्दी, pressure छाले can be बहुत मुश्किल to prevent in critically ill मरीजों, frail बड़ो, wheelchair उपयोक्ता ( विशेषकर जहाँ स्पाइनल injury is शामिल ) and terminally बीमार patients.
प्राथमिक रोकथाम is to redistribute pressure by turning the patient regularly.
The लाभ of turning to avoid further sores is खूब documented since at तनिक the 19th century.
in addition to turning और re-positioning the patient in bed or व्हीलचेयर, eating a संतुलित आहार साथ adequate प्रोटीन and keeping the स्किन फ़्री from exposure to मूत्र और स्टूल is बहुत important.
the व्यापकता of दबाव ulcers in hospital जमावट is high, लकिन सुधार are होने बना.
according to the 2010 ipup ( International Pressure अल्सर व्यापकता सर्वेक्षण ) conducted in Canada, वहीँ was a significant decrease in the overall facility-acquired व्यापकता of pressure छाले इससे 2009-2010.
छाले यहूद सबसे commonly पहचाना at the sacral/coccyx अल्सर स्थान ; however, एड़ी ulcers were the most common facility-acquired स्थान in the survey.

Luteinizing हार्मोन ( LH, also known as lutropin और sometimes lutrophin ) is a हार्मोन produced by gonadotroph cells in the अग्रवर्ती pituitary gland.
In females, an acute rise of lh ( `` lh surge '' ) triggers ovulation और development of the corpus luteum.

it acts synergistically with fsh.

stahlhelm ( बहुवचन, stahlhelme ) is German for `` steel हेल्मेट ''.
The इम्पीरियल German फौज began to बदलें the traditional boiled-leather pickelhaube ( spiked कॉम्बैट हेल्मेट ) with the stahlhelm दौरान World युद्ध i in 1916.
The term Stahlhelm refers both to a जेनेरिक स्टील helmet, and more specifically to the distinctive ( and iconic ) German design.
The stahlhelm, साथ इसके distinctive `` coal scuttle `` shape, was an instantly recognizable icon for सैन्य imagery and became a आम तत्व of सैन्य प्रचार on दोनो sides, बस जैसे the Pickelhaube before it.
Its name was भी प्रयुक्त by the Stahlhelm, a अर्धसैनिक राष्ट्रवादी संगठन स्थापित at the समाप्त of 1918.

फ्रैंकफर्ट विमानक्षेत्र serves as a hub नगर for लुफ़्थान्सा and receives फ़्लाइट इससे स्टार Alliance carriers.
Airline hubs are airports ranked as विशाल, medium, छोटी, and non-hubs as एक of the FAA विमानक्षेत्र श्रेणी which are re-evaluated every year आधारित on क्रमांक of वाणिज्यिक यात्री.
the अधिक common लकिन अनौपचारिक use लिये the phrase airline hub is an airport that an airline उपयोग as a transfer पाइंट to get passengers to उनके intended destination.
it is part of a हब और spoke model, जहाँ travelers चलती between एयरपोर्ट not परोसा by direct flights change planes en रूट to उनके destinations.
इस is as opposed to the पाइंट to पाइंट model.
अनेक hubs of the airlines are also situated at एयरपोर्ट in the शहरों of the respective head कार्यालयों.
Some एयरलाइंस may उपयोग only a single हब, while अन्य airlines उपयोग अनेक hubs.
hubs are प्रयुक्त लिये both यात्री flights as well as cargo फ़्लाइट.
Many airlines भी उपयोग फ़ोकस cities, which फलन much the वही as hubs.
Airlines may भी उपयोग secondary hubs, a non-technical पद for large फ़ोकस शहरों.
A हब in the मध्य of a रूट is more effective than at either end as connecting ट्रैफ़िक more easily fills the प्लेन - passengers prefer a one-stop ( two-leg ) रूट over a two-stop ( three-leg ) रूट.
खोखला Lacedaemon.
Site of the Menelaion, the shrine to हेलेन और Menelaus constructed anciently in the कांस्य आयु नगर that stood on the hill of therapne on the बाएँ बैंको of the eurotas नदी overlooking the भविष्य site of Dorian स्पार्टा.
आरपार the valley the successive ridges of Mount Taygetus हैं in evidence.
स्पार्टा ( doric Greek : ; अटारी यूनानी : ), or lacedaemon, थी a prominent city-state in प्राचीन Greece, situated on the banks of the eurotas River in laconia, in south-eastern Peloponnese.
it emerged as a political एंटिटी around the 10th century BC, when the आक्रमणकारी dorians subjugated the लोकल, non-Dorian population.
Around 650 bc, it रोज़ to become the dominant military land-power in ancient यूनानियों.
दिए its सैन्य pre-eminence, स्पार्टा was recognized as the overall leader of the संयुक्त यूनानी शक्तियां दौरान the greco-persian Wars.
between 431 और 404 bc, स्पार्टा थी the principal दुश्मन of एथेंस दौरान the Peloponnesian युद्ध, इससे which it emerged विजयी, though at ग्रेट cost.
स्पार्टा 's शिकस्त by thebes in the बैटल of leuctra in 371 BC ended Sparta 's prominent role in यूनानियों.
However, it कायम its राजनैतिक independence until the रोमन conquest of यूनानियों in 146 bc.
It then underwent a long period of मनाही, विशेषकर in the Middle आयु, जब many spartans moved to सजीव in mystras.
Modern Sparta is the capital of the यूनानी क्षेत्रीय ईकाई of laconia and a बीच for the processing of goods such as citrus और olives.
Sparta थी अद्वितीय in ancient यूनानियों लिये its social system and संविधान, जिससे completely focused on सैन्य प्रशिक्षण और excellence.
इसके निवासियों were वर्गीकृत as Spartiates ( Spartan नागरिकों, who enjoyed full अधिकारों ), Mothakes ( non-Spartan फ़्री मेन उठाया as spartans ), perioikoi ( freedmen ), और Helots ( state-owned serfs, enslaved non-spartan local population ).
Spartiates underwent the कठोर agoge training और शिक्षा regimen, and spartan phalanges were widely माना to be among the बेहतरीन in बैटल.
spartan महिलाओं enjoyed considerably अधिक rights और समता to men than elsewhere in the classical संसार.
Sparta थी the विषय of fascination in its अपना day, as खूब as in the वेस्ट following the पुनरुद्धार of classical learning.
इस प्रेम or admiration of स्पार्टा is ज्ञात as Laconism or laconophilia.

the world population is the कुल number of जीना humans on धरती.
as of आज, it is अनुमानित to क्रमांक अरब by the United राज्य जनसांख्यिकी ब्यूरो ( uscb ).
the USCB estimates कि the संसार जनसांख्यिकी exceeded 7 अरब on कूच 12, 2012.
according to a पृथक अनुमान by the संयुक्त राष्ट्र जनसांख्यिकी निधि, it पहुँचे this milestone on अक्तूबर 31, 2011.
the world population has experienced continuous विकास चूंकि the समाप्त of the ग्रेट Famine और the ब्लैक Death in 1350, जब it stood at around 370 लाख.
the उच्चतम rates of विकास – वैश्विक जनसांख्यिकी increases above 1.8 % प्रति year – were देखी briefly दौरान the 1950s, and for a longer period दौरान the 1960s and 1970s.
the growth रेट peaked at 2.2 % in 1963, and had अस्वीकृत to 1.1 % by 2011.
Total सालाना births यहूद highest in the late 1980s at about 138 million, and हैं अभी अपेक्षित to remain essentially constant at उनके 2011 स्तर of 134 million, जबकि deaths क्रमांक 56 लाख प्रति साल, और हैं अपेक्षित to बढ़ाएँ to 80 लाख per साल by 2040.
वर्तमान projections show a continued increase in जनसांख्यिकी in the near भविष्य ( but a स्थिर मनाही in the population growth rate ), with the global जनसांख्यिकी अपेक्षित to reach between 7.5 और 10.5 billion by 2050.
विभिन्न longer-term estimates भविष्यवाणी further growth, stagnation, or even overall मनाही in the global जनसांख्यिकी by 2150.
कुछ विश्लेषकों have questioned the स्थिरता of further संसार population growth, citing the growing pressures on the पर्यावरण, global खाना आपूर्तियाँ, and उर्जा संसाधन.
skeletal मांसपेशियां होमो sapiens
इस is a table of मांसपेशियां of the इंसान anatomy.
वहीँ हैं approximately 642 skeletal muscles भीतर the typical इंसान, और लगभग every मांसपेशी constitutes एक भाग of a जोड़ी of एकसमान bilateral muscles, found on दोनो पहलू, resulting in approximately 320 pairs of मांसपेशियां, as प्रस्तुत in इस आलेख.
Nevertheless, the सटीक क्रमांक is मुश्किल to define because अलग स्त्रोत समूह muscles differently, e.g. regarding कया is पारिभाषित as अलग भाग of a single मांसपेशी or as अनेक मांसपेशियां.
उदाहरण range इससे 640 to 850.
the मांसपेशियां of the इंसान body can be categorized into a number of समूह जिससे include मांसपेशियां relating to the सिर और गर्दन, मांसपेशियां of the धड़ or trunk, muscles of the अपर limbs, and muscles of the निम्नतर limbs.
the कार्रवाई refers to the कार्रवाई of प्रत्येक मांसपेशी from the standard anatomical स्थिति.
In अन्य positions, अन्य क्रियाएँ may be performed.
A सुनहरा बार is a मात्रा of refined metallic gold of any shape कि is made by a bar producer meeting मानक शर्तें of manufacture, labeling, and रिकार्ड keeping.
larger सुनहरा bars that are produced by pouring the molten metal into molds हैं पुकारा पिंडों.
छोटी bars may be manufactured by minting or stamping इससे appropriately लिपटे सुनहरा चादरें.
the मानक सुनहरा बार आयोजित as gold reserves by central banks और traded among bullion dealers is the 400-troy-ounce ( 12.4 kg or 438.9 औंस ) Good डिलीवरी gold बार.
the kilobar, which is to say 1000 गामा in द्रव्यमान, is the bar कि is more manageable and is प्रयुक्त extensively लिये व्यापार और निवेश.
the premium on ये bars when traded is very कम over the स्पॉट मान of the सुनहरा बनाना it आदर्श लिये छोटी transfers between बैंको और व्यापारियों.
Most kilobars are चपटा, although कुछ investors, particularly in Europe, prefer the ईंटों आकार.

वकालत is a political प्रक्रम by an individual or समूह which aims to influence public-policy and संसाधन आवंटन निर्णय within political, आर्थिक, and सोशल प्रणालियों and institutions.
वकालत can शामिल अनेक क्रियाएँ कि a व्यक्ति or संगठन undertakes including मीडिया अभियान, पब्लिक बोलना, commissioning और publishing शोध or पोल or the दाखिल of an amicus brief.
lobbying ( often by लॉबी समूह ) is a रूप of वकालत where a सीधा दृष्टिकोण is made to विधायक on an समस्या which plays a significant भूमिका in modern राजनीती.
शोध is beginning to explore how वकालत groups in the U.S. और कनाडा are using social मीडिया to सुकर नागरिक सगाई और collective कार्रवाई.
The ध्वज of मैक्सिको ( स्पेनी : bandera de México ) is a लंबवत तिरंगा of ग्रीन, white, और रेड साथ the national कोट of बाहें चार्ज in the center of the white stripe.
जबकि the अर्थ of the रंगों रै बदला over समय, these तीन colors were adopted by Mexico following स्वतंत्रता इससे स्पेन दौरान the देश 's War of स्वतंत्रता, और subsequent पहला मैक्सिकन साम्राज्य.
The वर्तमान flag थी adopted in 1968, लकिन the overall डिज़ाइन रै been प्रयुक्त since 1821, जब the पहला National ध्वज थी निर्मित.
The वर्तमान विधि of नेशनल symbols, Law on the National Arms, Flag, और गान, कि governs the उपयोग of the national flag रै महरूम in प्लेस since 1984.
रेड, white, and green हैं the रंगों of the national मुक्ति फौज in Mexico.
The सेंट्रल emblem is the एज़टेक pictogram for Tenochtitlan ( अभी मैक्सिको नगर ), the center of उनके साम्राज्य.
It recalls the legend that प्रेरित the Aztecs to settle on what थी originally a lake-island.
The रूप of the कोट of arms was most recently revised in 1968.
a रिबन in the national रंगों is at the नीचे of the coat of बाहें.

A गंतव्य विपणन संगठन or सम्मेलन और आगंतुक bureau promotes a कस्बा, नगर, प्रदेश, or देश in order to बढ़ाएँ the number of visitors.
it promotes the development and marketing of a destination, focusing on सम्मेलन बिक्री, पर्यटन marketing, और services.
Such संगठन promote आर्थिक विकास of a destination by increasing visits इससे tourists and business travelers, which generates overnight lodging लिये a गंतव्य, visits to restaurants, and खरीदारी revenues.
सम्मेलन and visitor bureaus are the most महत्वपूर्ण tourism विपणन organizations in उनके संबंधित पर्यटक गंतव्यों, as they हैं सीधे responsible for विपणन the गंतव्य ब्रांड through travel और पर्यटन `` product जागरूकता '' to visitors.
DMOs उपज अरबों of डॉलर in direct और अप्रत्यक्ष revenue और कर लिये their गंतव्यों ' economies with उनके विपणन and sales विशेषज्ञता.
गंतव्य विपणन organizations हैं प्रायः called travel, सम्मेलन, विज़िटर, or पर्यटन bureaux, स्वागत centers, सूचना centers और अधिक.
regardless of the नाम, ये संगठन प्रस्ताव अनेक सेवाएं to the traveling public.
The नीलगाय or wapiti ( cervus canadensis ) is एक of the largest प्रजाति of हिरण in the संसार, और एक of the largest land mammals in उत्तर अमेरिका और eastern एशिया.
It was long believed to be a subspecies of the यूरोपीय रेड हिरण ( cervus elaphus ), but प्रमाण from a 2004 पढ़ाई of the mitochondrial DNA indicates that the दो हैं पृथक species.
इस animal should नहीं be confused with the larger मूस ( alces alces ), to which the नाम `` elk '' applies in Eurasia.
Apart इससे the moose, the only other सदस्य of the deer family to प्रतिद्वंद्वी the नीलगाय in size is the दक्षिण Asian sambar ( Rusa unicolor ).
नीलगाय दायरा in forest and forest-edge आवास, feeding on grasses, पौधे, leaves, और छाल.
हालांकि देशी to North अमेरिका और eastern एशिया, वे have adapted well to देशों where they have महरूम introduced, सहित Argentina, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, and New जीलैंड.
Their ग्रेट adaptability may threaten endemic प्रजाति और ecosystems into जिससे वे have महरूम introduced.
Male elk have विशाल antlers जिससे हैं शेड प्रत्येक साल.
Males भी engage in ritualized समागम व्यवहार दौरान the rut, सहित posturing, antler कुश्ती ( sparring ), और bugling, a loud श्रेणी of vocalizations जिससे establishes दबदबा over अन्य males और attracts महिलाओं.
नीलगाय are susceptible to a क्रमांक of infectious diseases, कुछ of which can be transmitted to livestock.
प्रयत्न to eliminate infectious रोगों from elk populations, largely through vaccination, have था मिश्रित success.
कुछ संस्कृतियों आदर the elk as a आध्यात्मिक force.
In भाग of एशिया, antlers और their velvet are प्रयुक्त in परंपरागत दवाइयाँ.
नीलगाय are hunted as a game species ; the meat is leaner and उच्चतर in प्रोटीन than बीफ or मुर्गा.
The जार्ज वॉशिंगटन विश्वविद्यालयों ( gw, gwu, or George Washington ) is a व्यापक निजी, coeducational शोध विश्वविद्यालयों located in वॉशिंगटन, d.C..

the lion ( पेंथेरा leo ) is one of the four big बिल्लियों in the genus पेंथेरा and a सदस्य of the परिवार Felidae.
With some males exceeding in weight, it is the second-largest जीना बिल्ली बाद the tiger.
जंगली शेर फिलहाल मौजूद in sub-saharan Africa और in एशिया ( जहाँ an endangered remnant जनसांख्यिकी resides in Gir वन नेशनल पार्क in इण्डिया ) while अन्य types of lions have disappeared इससे North Africa and दक्षिणपश्चिम एशिया in ऐतिहासिक times.
Until the late pleistocene, परिचय 10,000 years पहले, the lion थी the most फैली विशाल जमीन mammal बाद इंसानो.
वे were मिला in सबसे of अफ़्रीकी, आरपार Eurasia इससे western Europe to India, और in the Americas इससे the Yukon to पेरू.
The lion is a vulnerable species, having देखी a प्रमुख जनसांख्यिकी decline of 30–50 % over the past दो decades in its अफ़्रीकी दायरा.
शेर populations हैं untenable outside designated reserves और नेशनल पार्क.
Although the कारण of the मनाही is नहीं fully understood, आवास loss and conflicts साथ humans are फिलहाल the greatest कल्याणकारी of concern.
भीतर Africa, the West अफ़्रीकी lion जनसांख्यिकी is विशेषकर endangered.
Lions live लिये 10–14 सालो in the wild, while in captivity वे can सजीव longer than 20 years.
in the wild, males seldom सजीव longer than 10 सालो, as चोटों sustained इससे continual fighting साथ प्रतिद्वंद्वी males greatly reduce उनके आयु.
वे typically inhabit सवाना और घासभूमि, although वे may take to बुश and forest.
Lions हैं unusually सोशल compared to अन्य cats.
a pride of शेर consists of सम्बन्धित females और offspring and a छोटी क्रमांक of वयस्क males.
Groups of मादा lions typically hunt साथ, preying ज़्यादातर on विशाल ungulates.
शेर हैं apex and keystone परभक्षी, हालांकि they scavenge as opportunity allows.
जबकि शेर do नहीं typically hunt इंसानो, some have महरूम known to do so.
sleeping मुख्यतः दौरान the दिन, शेर are primarily nocturnal, although bordering on crepuscular in प्रकृति.
अत्यधिक distinctive, the male lion is easily recognised by its माने, and इसके face is one of the most widely recognised animal प्रतीकों in इंसान संस्कृति.
depictions have existed from the अपर paleolithic काल, साथ carvings and paintings इससे the lascaux और chauvet गुफाएं, through वस्तुतः सब प्राचीन और medieval संस्कृतियों where वे once occurred.
it रै been extensively चित्रित in sculptures, in paintings, on नेशनल flags, and in समकालीन films और साहित्य.

Zoos are cooperating worldwide in breeding कार्यक्रम for the endangered Asiatic subspecies.

starting with हैंडहेल्ड consoles, the seventh generation began on 21 November 2004 साथ the उत्तर अमरीकी परिचय of the निन्टेंडो ds as a `` third pillar '', alongside निन्टेंडो 's existing खेल लड़के Advance and GameCube consoles.

Sgt. pepper 's निर्जन Hearts Club बैंड ( often shortened to sgt. pepper ) is the eighth studio album by English rock band the बीटल्स.
released in जून 1967, the एल्बम शामिल songs such as `` साथ a Little सहायता from My मित्रों ``, `` लुसी in the आसमान साथ ईंट ``, and `` A दिन in the जीवन ``.
Continuing the artistic maturation seen on the band 's album Revolver ( 1966 ), Sgt. Pepper further रजि इससे the conventional pop चट्टान मुहावरा of the समय और incorporated balladry, साइकेडेलिक, म्यूज़िक hall, and symphonic प्रभाव.
During the Sgt. pepper sessions, the समूह improved upon the विशेषता of उनके music 's production while exploring प्रायोगिक रिकॉर्डिंग तकनीकों.
Producer जार्ज मार्टिन 's अभिनव approach शामिल the use of an ऑर्केस्ट्रा.
Widely acclaimed और imitated, the एल्बम cover, designed by अंग्रेज़ी पॉप कलाकारों पीटर ब्लेक and Jann Haworth, थी प्रेरित by a sketch by पॉल McCartney कि चित्रित the band posing in सामने of a कोलाज of कुछ of उनके favourite celebrities.
Sgt. pepper थी a विश्वव्यापी critical और वाणिज्यिक कामयाबी, बिता 27 सप्ताह at the शीर्ष of the uk एल्बम Chart and 15 सप्ताह at number एक on the US बिलबोर्ड 200.
a seminal कार्य in the उभरते साइकेडेलिक चट्टान style, the एल्बम was critically acclaimed upon release और won four Grammy पुरस्कार in 1968.
With an estimated 32 million copies बेची, it is one of the संसार 's best selling albums.
Sgt. pepper is माना by अनेक to be the most influential and प्रसिद्ध चट्टान एल्बम कभी, और रै been named the महानतम एल्बम of सब समय by दोनो सब Time शीर्ष 1000 एल्बम और रोलिंग स्टोन.
the temporal पालि is a प्रदेश of the दिमागी cortex that is located beneath the पार्श्ववर्ती fissure on both cerebral बांटती of the mammalian brain.
the temporal lobes हैं involved in the retention of विज़ुअल यादें, प्रसंस्करण संवेदी इनपुट, comprehending भाषा, storing new memories, emotion, और deriving meaning.
The human lungs are the अंगों of respiration in इंसानो.
Humans have दो फेफड़े, a सही lung और a बाएँ फेफड़ों.
the सही lung consists of तीन lobes जबकि the बाएँ lung is slightly छोटी consisting of only two निर्मोक ( the बाएँ lung रै a `` हृदय पायदान '' allowing स्पेस लिये the heart भीतर the chest ).
Together, the lungs contain लगभग of एयरवेज़ and 300 to 500 million alveoli, having a कुल सतह क्षेत्रफल of परिचय ( ) in वयस्कों — roughly the same क्षेत्रफल as one side of a टेनिस अदालत.
furthermore, if all of the capillaries that घेर the alveoli यहूद unwound और laid समाप्त to समाप्त, वे होता extend for about.
प्रत्येक फेफड़ों weighs, therefore making the संपूर्ण अंग about.
Human फेफड़े
the श्वासनली divides into two bronchi ( one for प्रत्येक side ) at the स्तर of t4.
इस junction is also known as the carina.
The conducting zone contains the trachea, the bronchi, the bronchioles, और the टर्मिनल bronchioles the respiratory zone contains the respiratory bronchioles, the alveolar नलिकाएं, and the alveoli.
the conducting मण्डल and the respiratory stuffers ( लकिन not the alveoli ) हैं made up of airways.
the conducting मण्डल रै no gas एक्सचेंज साथ the रक्त, और is reinforced साथ cartilage in अनुक्रम to थाम open the एयरवेज़.
the conducting मण्डल warms the एयर to और humidifies the एयर.
It also cleanses the air by निकालना अणु via cilia located on the walls of all the passageways.
The फेफड़े हैं घिरी by the पसली cage.
the respiratory zone is the साईट of gas exchange साथ रक्त.
The sympathetic बेचैन system via noradrenaline एक्टिंग on the beta receptors कल्याणकारी bronchodilation.
the parasympathetic nervous system via acetylcholine, which अधिनियमों on the M-3 muscarinic receptors, maintains the resting टोन of the bronchiolar smooth मांसपेशी.
इस कार्रवाई is सम्बन्धित, हालांकि considered distinct from bronchoconstriction.
अनेक other non-autonomic बेचैन और biochemical stimuli, सहित carbon dioxide और ऑक्सीजन, हैं भी शामिल in the विनियमन प्रक्रम.

the red-eye प्रभाव in छायाचित्र is the आम रूप of red pupils in रंग photographs of आँखें.
