The University of कैलिफ़ोर्निया, सांता बारबरा ( commonly referred to as UC सांता बारबरा or UCSB ) is a पब्लिक शोध विश्वविद्यालयों और one of the ten सामान्य campuses of the University of California प्रणाली.
The प्रमुख कैम्पस is located on a साईट in Goleta, कैलिफ़ोर्निया, संयुक्त States, इससे Santa Barbara और उत्तरपश्चिम of लॉस एंजिल्स.
Tracing इसके roots back to 1891 as an independent शिक्षक ' college, UCSB joined the University of कैलिफ़ोर्निया प्रणाली in 1944 और is the third-oldest general-education campus in the प्रणाली.
ucsb is एक of America 's Public आइवी universities, which recognizes top पब्लिक research विश्वविद्यालयों in the संयुक्त States.
the university is a comprehensive डॉक्टरेट विश्वविद्यालयों और is व्यवस्थित into पाँच कॉलेजों and schools offering 87 undergraduate डिग्री और 55 ग्रैजुएट degrees.
The कैम्पस is the 6th-largest in the UC प्रणाली by enrollment साथ 18,977 undergraduate और 2,950 ग्रैजुएट students.
in 2012, ucsb थी ranked 41st among `` नेशनल विश्वविद्यालयों '' और 10th among public universities by U.S. न्यूज & संसार रपट.
The विश्वविद्यालयों थी also ranked 35th विश्वव्यापी by the टाइम्स उच्चतर Education World विश्वविद्यालयों rankings and 34th worldwide ( 6th worldwide लिये engineering ) by the अकादमिक रैंकिंग of संसार विश्वविद्यालयों in 2012. < संदर्भ name= '' shanghairanking.com/fieldeng2012 '' >
uc सांता Barbara is a `` very high activity '' research विश्वविद्यालयों और खर्च $ 191.2 लाख on शोध expenditures in the 2007 फिस्कल year, 97th-largest in the संयुक्त राज्य.

संत जोसेफ साथ the शिशु यीशु by Guido reni
संत जोसेफ 's दिन, March 19, the Feast of st. Joseph is in पश्चिमी christianity the principal feast day of संत Joseph, जीवनसाथी of the धन्य Virgin मरियम.
he is भी the step-father of यीशु of नासरत /Jesus Christ.
it रै the रैंक of a solemnity in the रोमन कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर ; catholics जो follow the Missal of 1962 celebrate it as a पहला क्लास feast.
पिछला to 1962 it was मनाये as a feast of the rank of दोगुना of the पहला class.
it is a feast or commemoration in the provinces of the anglican नियाज़, और a feast or पर्व in the लूथरन Church.
संत जोसेफ 's दिन is the Patronal Feast day for Poland as खूब as for कनाडा, व्यक्तियों named जोसेफ, josephine, etc., for धार्मिक institutes, स्कूलों और parishes bearing उसके नाम, और for बढ़ई.
it is also पिता 's Day in कुछ कैथोलिक countries, mainly Spain, Portugal, और Italy.
March 19 थी समर्पित to Saint जोसेफ in several पश्चिमी पंचांग by the दसवाँ century, and इस custom was स्थापित in रोम by 1479.
Pope St. पायस v extended इसके use to the संपूर्ण रोमन रीति by उसके अपोस्टोलिक Constitution quo primum ( July 14, 1570 ).
चूंकि 1969, एपिस्कोपल सम्मेलनों may, if they काश, ट्रांसफ़र it to a date outside lent.
Between 1870 and 1955, a feast was celebrated in सम्मान of st. जोसेफ as Spouse of the धन्य वर्जिन मरियम and Patron of the सार्वभौमिक Church, the latter शीर्षक having महरूम दिए to उसे by पोप पायस ix.
Originally मनाये on the तीसरा संडे बाद ईस्टर साथ an octave, बाद divino Afflatu of st. पायस x ( see सुधार of the रोमन breviary by Pope Pius x ), it was स्थानांतरित to the preceding बुधवार.
the feast थी also retitled the solemnity of संत जोसेफ.
इस जश्न और इसके accompanying अष्टक थी abolished दौरान the modernisation और सरलीकरण of rubrics अंतर्गत Pope पायस बारहवीं in 1955.
It is स्टिल कायम by Catholics who follow the missal of 1962 or पहले missals.
as the परंपरागत holiday of the Apostles ss. फिलिप और जेम्स, May 1, था धुंधली from the memory of सबसे catholics by the mid-twentieth सदी, that of Joseph the Worker थी created in order to coincide साथ the जश्न of international श्रमिक Day ( May दिन ) in many countries.
The feast of ss. Philip and जेम्स, जिससे had महरूम celebrated on कि तिथि चूंकि the sixth सदी, थी स्थानांतरित इससे its traditional प्लेस.
in the new calendar published in 1969, the feast, जिससे at one time occupied the उच्चतम संभावित rank in the Church पंचांग, थी घटाया to an वैकल्पिक Memorial, the न्यूनतम rank लिये a संत 's दिन.

mariah Carey ( born कूच 27, 1970 ) is an American singer, songwriter, रिकार्ड producer, अभिनेत्री, और philanthropist.
अंतर्गत the guidance of कोलंबिया रिकॉर्ड कार्यपालिका टॉमी Mottola, Carey released उसके self-titled debut स्टुडियो एल्बम mariah कैरी in 1990 ; it went multi-platinum और spawned four consecutive क्रमांक एक singles on the u.s. Billboard hot 100 चार्ट.
following her marriage to mottola in 1993 और success साथ hit रिकॉर्ड भाव ( 1991 ), Music बक्सा ( 1993 ), and मैरी क्रिसमस ( 1994 ), Carey was established as Columbia 's highest-selling act.
Daydream ( 1995 ) बना music history when इसके दूसरी सिंगल `` एक Sweet Day ``, a duet साथ Boyz II Men, spent a रिकार्ड सोलह सप्ताह on शीर्ष of the बिलबोर्ड Hot 100, और remains the longest-running number-one सोंग in u.S. chart इतिहास.
दौरान the recording of the एल्बम, Carey began to deviate from her r & b और पॉप beginnings and धीरे traversed into हिप hop.
इस musical बदलें became evident साथ the release of Butterfly ( 1997 ), at which समय Carey had अलग इससे mottola.
कैरी बाएँ Columbia in 2000, और हस्ताक्षरित a record-breaking $ 100 million रिकॉर्डिंग अनुबंध with वर्जिन रिकॉर्ड.
पहले the release of her पहला विशेषता film glitter ( 2001 ), वो suffered a physical और emotional विश्लेषण और was hospitalized लिये कठोर थकावट.
Following the फिल्मी 's ग़रीब रिसेप्शन, she was खरीदा आउट of her recording अनुबंध लिये $ 50 लाख, which led to a decline in उसके करियर.
She हस्ताक्षरित a multi-million डालर contract सौदे साथ द्वीप Records in 2002, and after an unsuccessful period, लौटे to the शीर्ष of music चार्ट with The emancipation of मिमी ( 2005 ).
इसके second सिंगल `` We Belong Together `` became उसके सबसे successful सिंगल of the 2000s, और थी later नामित `` Song of the Decade '' by बिलबोर्ड.
कैरी एकबार again ventured into film with a well-received starring भूमिका in ( 2009 ) ; वो was awarded the `` भेदन प्रदर्शन पुरस्कार '' at the ताड़ Springs International फिल्मी पर्व, और Black रील और NAACP Image Award nominations.
in a करियर spanning over दो दशकों, कैरी has बेची more than 200 लाख records worldwide, बनाना उसके एक of the best-selling म्यूज़िक artists of सब time.
In 1998, she थी honored as the संसार 's best-selling रिकॉर्डिंग कलाकार of the 1990s at the संसार म्यूज़िक पुरस्कार.
कैरी was also नामित the best-selling मादा artist of the millennium in 2000.
according to the Recording Industry Association of अमेरिका, she is the तीसरा best-selling female कलाकार in the संयुक्त States, with 63.5 लाख certified एल्बम.
साथ the रिलीज of `` Touch my देह `` ( 2008 ), कैरी gained उसके eighteenth number एक single in the संयुक्त States, अधिक than कोई अन्य solo कलाकार.
in 2012, कैरी थी क्रमित दूसरी on VH1 's सूची of the `` 100 महानतम महिलाओं in Music ''.
Aside from उसके वाणिज्यिक accomplishments, कैरी has won पाँच Grammy Awards, 17 संसार Music पुरस्कार, 11 अमरीकी Music पुरस्कार, and 31 Billboard म्यूज़िक पुरस्कार.
referred to as the `` songbird परम् '' by the Guinness संसार रिकॉर्ड, वो is famed for her five-octave गायन range, power, melismatic style and signature use of the whistle register.
A bumblebee is any member of the मधुमक्खी genus Bombus, in the परिवार Apidae.
There are over 250 known species, existing primarily in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध हालांकि they भी occur in South America.
They have महरूम introduced to नई Zealand और the ऑस्ट्रेलियाई राज्य of तस्मानिया.
Bumblebees are social कीट कि are characterised by black and yellow देह बालों, often in bands.
However, some species have orange or red on their bodies, or may be entirely black.
Another स्पष्ट ( but नहीं unique ) characteristic is the नरम nature of the बाल ( long, branched setae ), called pile, कि कवर उनके संपूर्ण body, making उन्हें appear और महसूस फजी.
वे are best विशिष्ट from similarly विशाल, फजी मधुमक्खियों by the रूप of the मादा हिन्द leg, which is परिवर्धित to रूप a corbicula : a चमकदार concave सतह that is bare, लकिन घिरी by a फ्रिंज of hairs प्रयुक्त to हस्तांतरण पराग ( in similar bees, the हिन्द leg is completely बालदार, और pollen दाने are wedged into the बालों for हस्तांतरण ).
Like उनके रिश्तेदारों the honey bees, bumblebees feed on nectar and एकत्रित pollen to feed उनके यंग.
A man openly carrying a handgun in a बर्गर किंग in Eagle, Colorado.
In the संयुक्त राज्य, खोलें carry is shorthand शब्दावली लिये `` खुलकर carrying a firearm in पब्लिक '', as distinguished from concealed carry, जहाँ firearms can नहीं be seen by the कैज़ुअल observer.
The अभ्यास of खोलें carry, जहाँ gun स्वामी openly carry firearms जबकि they go परिचय उनके रोज़ कारोबार, has seen an increase in the U.S. in recent सालो.
इस रै been marked by a क्रमांक of व्यवस्थित कार्यक्रम intended to बढ़ाएँ the दृश्यता of open carry and public awareness about the अभ्यास.
proponents of open carry point to history और आंकडे, noting कि अपराधियों प्रायः छिपाते their weapons.
प्रोत्साहित by groups like opencarry.org, georgiacarry.org और कुछ भागीदार of the Free राज्य Project, खोलें carry रै seen a revival in recent सालो, लकिन it is नहीं yet clear if this represents बस a short-term ट्रेंड.
the गन अधिकारों जातियाँ रै महरूम mixed in इसके जवाब.
एलन Gottlieb of the दूसरी amendment न्यास and the nra have महरूम cautious in expressing support, while special-interest समूह ऐसे as the aforementioned opencarry.org and georgiacarry.org, और certain national groups such as the Gun स्वामी of America ( गोवा ) have महरूम अधिक outspoken in एहसान of the अभ्यास.
खोलें carry is strongly opposed by gun control समूह ऐसे as the ब्रैडी अभियान और the गठबन्धन to Stop गन हिंसा.

the grafenrheinfeld नाभिकीय शक्ति संयंत्र in जर्मनी.
चांसलर Angela Merkel 's गठबन्धन announced on May 30, 2011, कि germany’s 17 नाभिकीय शक्ति stations will be shut bas by 2022, in a नीति reversal following जापानी 's Fukushima Daiichi नाभिकीय disaster.
फिलहाल, 68 रिएक्टरों हैं under निर्माण in 15 countries.
Nuclear शक्ति stations operate in thirty countries.
In 2010, before the फुकुशिमा daiichi nuclear disaster, it थी reported that an average of about 10 नाभिकीय रिएक्टरों were अपेक्षित to become operational per year, although according to the संसार Nuclear संघ, of the 17 civilian reactors नियोजित to become operational between 2007 and 2009, तभी पाँच दरअसल आए on स्ट्रीम.
as of जून 2011, Germany और स्विट्ज़रलैंड are phasing-out नाभिकीय शक्ति.
as of June 2011, देशों ऐसे as ऑस्ट्रेलिया, ऑस्ट्रिया, डेनमार्क, यूनानियों, आयरलैंड, इटली, लातवियाई, liechtenstein, ध्वज, मलेशिया, Malta, New Zealand, Norway और Portugal remain opposed to nuclear शक्ति.
Color गति picture film refers both to unexposed रंग फ़ोटोग्राफ़िक फिल्मी in a स्वरूप suitable for use in a motion picture कैमरा, और to finished motion चित्र फिल्मी, ready लिये उपयोग in a प्रोजेक्टर, which bears बिंब in color.
the first रंग cinematography was by means of additive color systems such as the one patented in England by Edward रेमंड टर्नर in 1899 और tested in 1902.
a simplified additive प्रणाली थी developed by George अल्बर्ट स्मिथ और successfully commercialized in 1909 as kinemacolor.
ये early systems used black-and-white फिल्मी to फोटोग्राफ और प्रोजेक्ट दो or more घटक बिंब through अलग रंग फ़िल्टर.
Still from फुटेज अंकित by Edward टर्नर in 1902
With the present-day प्रौद्योगिकी, वहीँ हैं two पृथक प्रक्रियाओं : Eastman रंग ऋणात्मक 2 chemistry ( कैमरा ऋणात्मक स्टॉक्स, duplicating interpositive and internegative स्टॉक्स ) and Eastman Color धनात्मक 2 रसायन ( positive prints for direct projection ), usually abbreviated as ecn-2 और ecp-2.
Fuji 's उत्पाद हैं compatible with ecn-2 और ecp-2.

The United States Army एयर Forces ( USAAF or AAF ) was the सैन्य विमानन भुजा of the United States of अमेरिका during and तत्काल बाद World War ii, and the direct पूर्ववर्ती of the संयुक्त States एयर फ़ोर्स.
the aaf थी a घटक of the संयुक्त राज्य फौज, जिससे in 1942 थी विभाजित functionally by कार्यपालिका अनुक्रम into three autonomous forces : the फौज मैदान शक्तियां, the Services of Supply ( which in 1943 became the फौज सेवा शक्तियां ), and the AAF.
Each of ये forces था a commanding general जो reported directly to the मुख्य of Staff of the संयुक्त राज्य फौज.
The aaf administered सब parts of सैन्य aviation formerly distributed among the फौज Air Corps, सामान्य मुख्यालय एयर Force, और मैदान forces corps area कमांडरों, और thus became the पहला air संगठन of the U.S. Army to कंट्रोल इसके अपना संस्थापना and support कर्मियों.
In practice, the AAF थी वस्तुतः autonomous inside the Army.
The शिखर आकार of the aaf was over 2.4 लाख मेन and महिलाओं in सेवा and nearly 80,000 वायुयान in 1944, and 783 घरेलू bases in December 1943.
by ve Day it had 1.25 लाख मेन stationed overseas and संचालित from अधिक than 1,600 airfields विश्वव्यापी.
the एयर Corps became the फौज एयर शक्तियां in जून 1941 to provide the एयर arm a greater स्वायत्तता in जिससे to expand more efficiently, and to provide a ढांचा लिये the अतिरिक्त command echelons required by a vastly increased force.
Although अन्य राष्ट्र already था separate एयर शक्तियां independent of the फौज or नेवी ( ऐसे as the अंग्रेजों Royal एयर फ़ोर्स and the German luftwaffe ), the AAF remained a भाग of the संयुक्त राज्य फौज until the United राज्य Air फ़ोर्स came into being in September 1947.
However, in its विस्तार और conduct of the war, the aaf became more than बस an arm of the वृहद organization.
by the समाप्त of संसार War ii the aaf था become virtually an स्वतंत्र service.
by regulation और कार्यपालिका अनुक्रम, the AAF थी a subordinate एजेंसी of the युद्ध विभाग tasked तभी साथ आयोजन, training, and equipping combat इकाई, limited in जिम्मेदारी to the महाद्वीपीय संयुक्त राज्य, as यहूद the फौज मैदान शक्तियां और the फौज सेवा शक्तियां.
in वास्तविकता, Headquarters AAF controlled the conduct of सब पहलुओं of the air war in every भाग of the संसार, determining air नीति और issuing आदेश बगैर transmitting उन्हें through the मुख्य of Staff.
इस `` कंट्रास्ट between theory और फैक्ट is... fundamental to an understanding of the aaf. ''
the Freedom of सूचना अधिनियम ( FOIA ) is a संघीय स्वतंत्रता of information विधि that allows लिये the full or आंशिक प्रकटीकरण of previously unreleased information and दस्तावेज़ नियंत्रित by the संयुक्त States सरकारी.
The अधिनियम defines एजेंसी records विषय to प्रकटीकरण, outlines अनिवार्य प्रकटीकरण प्रक्रियाओं और grants नौ छूटों to the statute.
it थी originally हस्ताक्षरित into law by अध्यक्ष lyndon B. जॉनसन, despite उसके misgivings, on July 4, 1966 as and went into प्रभाव the following साल.
the Federal Government 's स्वतंत्रता of सूचना अधिनियम should not be उलझन साथ the different and varying स्वतंत्रता of सूचना Acts passed by the व्यक्तिगत राज्य.
अनेक of those राज्य acts may be समान लकिन not identical to the संघीय act.
the European संघ ( eu ) is an economic और राजनैतिक संघ of 27 member राज्य कि are located primarily in Europe.
The EU operates through a प्रणाली of supranational स्वतंत्र संस्थानों and intergovernmental negotiated निर्णय by the सदस्य राज्य.
संस्थानों of the EU शामिल the यूरोपीय Commission, the परिषद of the यूरोपीय संघ, the यूरोपीय Council, the Court of इंसाफ of the यूरोपीय संघ, the यूरोपीय Central बैंको, the Court of auditors, and the यूरोपीय पार्लियामेंट.
the European पार्लियामेंट is निर्वाचित every five years by eu नागरिकों.
the eu 's de facto पूंजी is ब्रसेल्स.
The EU traces इसके origins इससे the European कोयले और स्टील जातियाँ ( ecsc ) and the यूरोपीय आर्थिक जातियाँ ( eec ), formed by the Inner Six देशों in 1951 and 1958 क्रमशः.
In the intervening years the जातियाँ and its successors have grown in size by the accession of नई member राज्य और in शक्ति by the जोड of नीति क्षेत्रों to its remit.
The maastricht Treaty स्थापित the यूरोपीय Union under इसके वर्तमान नाम in 1993.
the latest प्रमुख amendment to the constitutional basis of the EU, the Treaty of लिस्बन, came into फ़ोर्स in 2009.
The EU रै विकसित a सिंगल market through a standardised प्रणाली of laws कि apply in सब सदस्य states.
Within the Schengen Area ( जिससे शामिल 22 EU और 4 non-EU राज्य ) passport controls have been abolished.
EU नीतियों aim to ensure the फ़्री गति of लोगों, goods, सेवाएं, और capital, enact विधान in इंसाफ और home अफेयर्स, और maintain आम नीतियों on व्यापार, कृषि, fisheries और क्षेत्रीय विकास.
a मौद्रिक union, the eurozone, थी स्थापित in 1999 और is composed of 17 member states.
Through the आम Foreign and सुरक्षा नीति the eu रै developed a भूमिका in बाह्य संबंध और रक्षा.
स्थाई diplomatic मिशन have been established around the world.
the EU is represented at the United Nations, the WTO, the G8 और the G-20.
With a संयुक्त जनसांख्यिकी of over 500 लाख निवासियों, or 7.3 % of the world जनसांख्यिकी, the EU, in 2012, उत्पन्न a nominal सकल घरेलू उत्पाद ( जीडीपी ) of 16.584 trillion us डॉलर, representing approximately 20 % of the वैश्विक जीडीपी when measured in terms of खरीदना power पैरिटी, और represents the largest नाममात्र जीडीपी and जीडीपी PPP in the संसार.
the eu was the प्राप्तकर्ता of the 2012 नोबेल Peace पुरस्कार.
the वेल्स नेशनल rugby लीग team represent Wales in international रग्बी league फ़ुटबॉल मिलान.

Cardiomyopathy ( वस्तुतः `` heart muscle बीमारी '' ) is the measurable deterioration of the फलन of the myocardium ( the दिल मांसपेशी ) for any reason, प्रायः leading to दिल विफलता ; आम symptoms are dyspnea ( breathlessness ) और परिधीय edema ( सूजन of the टाँगे ).
लोगों with cardiomyopathy हैं प्रायः at रिस्क of खतरनाक फ़ॉर्म of irregular heart ताल और अचानक cardiac मौत.
the सबसे आम form of cardiomyopathy is dilated cardiomyopathy.
Fuck in इसके शाब्दिक अर्थ refers to the अधिनियम of यौन मैथुन.
it is an English word कि is प्रायः प्रयुक्त as a profanity, either to denote तिरस्कार or as an intensifier.
The origin of the शब्द is अस्पष्ट.
It is usually considered to be पहला attested to around 1475, but it may be considerably पुरानी.
in आधुनिक उपयोग, fuck और its derivatives ( ऐसे as कमीने और fucking ) can be used in the position of a noun, a क्रिया, an क्रियाशील or an adverb.
वहीँ are अनेक आम phrases which मेक उपयोग of the word, as खूब as a क्रमांक of यौगिकों incorporating it, such as motherfucker.

Clinical प्रयोगशाला in a हॉस्पिटल सेटिंग showing several स्वचालित analysers.
A medical प्रयोगशाला or clinical laboratory is a प्रयोगशाला where tests हैं किया on clinical नमूनों in अनुक्रम to मिलेंगी सूचना परिचय the health of a रोगी as pertaining to the निदान, उपचार, and रोकथाम of disease.
in पोकर, players construct हैंड्स of पाँच ताश according to predetermined rules, which vary according to जिससे variant of पोकर is being निभाई.
ये हैंड्स हैं compared using a हाथ ranking प्रणाली that is standard across all variants of पोकर, the खिलाड़ी साथ the highest-ranking हाथ winning that particular deal in most variants of poker.
in some विसंगतियाँ, the lowest-ranking hand can win or tie.
These हाथ rankings हैं भी प्रयुक्त in some other कार्ड खेल, और in पोकर dice.
The ranking of a particular हाथ is increased by सहित अनेक cards of the वही कार्ड रैंक, by सब five ताश होने from the same suit, or by all पाँच cards being of consecutive रैंक.
the सापेक्ष ranking of the विभिन्न hand श्रेणी is based on the संभाव्यता of being randomly dealt such a हाथ इससे a well- shuffled डेक.
ब्रूस रान्डेल hornsby ( born नवम्बर 23, 1954 ) is an American virtuoso ; a singer, pianist, सिंथेसाइज़र, accordion, और dulcimer खिलाड़ी, and songwriter.
ज्ञात for the spontaneity and creativity of his live प्रदर्शन, hornsby draws अक्सर from classical, jazz, bluegrass, folk, motown, gospel, चट्टान, blues, और jam बैंड musical परंपराओं साथ उसके songwriting और the seamless improvisations contained भीतर.
hornsby 's रिकार्डिंग have been recognised on a number of occasions साथ उद्योग पुरस्कार, including the बेहतरीन New Artist Grammy in 1987 साथ ब्रूस hornsby and the Range, the Best ब्लूग्रास Recording ग्रैमी in 1990, और the बेहतरीन Pop इंस्ट्रूमेंटल ग्रैमी in 1993.
hornsby has भी हासिल recognition लिये उसके सोलो एल्बम and performances, his touring बैंड Bruce Hornsby और the noisemakers, उसके bluegrass प्रोजेक्ट with रिकी skaggs और उसके दिखावे as a session- और guest-musician.
He भी collaborated with आभारी मुर्दे and was a member of the बैंड from September 1990 to March 1992, playing at over one सौ shows during that काल.
गन्ना plantation in ग्रामीण क्यूबा
Agriculture in Cuba has निभाई an महत्वपूर्ण part in the अर्थव्यवस्था लिये अनेक hundred सालो.
कृषि contributes कम than 10 प्रतिशत to the सकल domestic उत्पाद ( जीडीपी ), लकिन it employs roughly 20 प्रतिशत of the working population.
परिचय 30 percent of the country 's जमीन is used लिये क्रॉप cultivation.
the inefficient agricultural उद्योग in क्यूबा रै led to the need to आयात विशाल amounts of भोजन.
क्यूबा now imports परिचय 80 % of the खाना it rations to the पब्लिक.
the rationing program खाते लिये परिचय a third of the खाना energy the औसत Cuban consumes.

u.S. महिलाओं suffragists demonstrating for the सही to vote, February 1913.
महिलाओं 's suffrage also ज्ञात as स्त्री suffrage is the सही of women to vote and to चलाएं लिये दफ्तर.
सीमित voting अधिकारों यहूद gained by women in Sweden, फिनलैंड और कुछ पश्चिमी u.S. राज्य in the लेट 19th century.
International संगठन यहूद formed to coordinate प्रयत्न, especially the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Council of Women ( 1888 ) और the अंतरराष्ट्रीय स्त्री suffrage Alliance ( 1904 ).
In 1893, नई जीलैंड, तब a self-governing British उपनिवेश, granted adult महिलाओं the सही to vote और the self-governing British colony of South ऑस्ट्रेलिया did the वही in 1895, लकिन भी permitted महिलाओं to run लिये दफ्तर.
ऑस्ट्रेलिया federated in 1901, और महिलाओं acquired the सही to vote and स्टैंड in federal चुनावों इससे 1902, though uneven restrictions on aboriginal महिलाओं voting in national चुनावों यहूद नहीं completely removed जबतक 1962.
the पहला European देश to introduce women 's suffrage was the Grand Duchy of Finland, तब part of the रूसी Empire, जिससे भी produced the world 's first मादा सदस्यों of पार्लियामेंट in the 1907 parliamentary चुनावों.
नार्वे followed, granting पूरा महिलाओं 's suffrage in 1913.
In सबसे पश्चिमी देशों, women 's suffrage आए बाद संसार i War i i, with कुछ important लेट अनुकूलक होने फ़्रांस in 1944 और Switzerland in 1971.
महिलाओं 's suffrage रै generally महरूम पहचाना after राजनैतिक campaigns to obtain it यहूद waged.
in अनेक देशों it थी granted पहले सार्वभौमिक suffrage.
Women 's suffrage is explicitly stated as a सही अंतर्गत the Convention on the विलोपन of All Forms of पक्षपात Against महिलाओं, अपनाया by the United राष्ट्र in 1979.

Jehovah 's गवाह is a millenarian restorationist ईसाई denomination साथ nontrinitarian मान्यताओं पृथक इससे mainstream Christianity.सोर्सs for descriptors : • millenarian : • restorationist : • Christian : • Denomination : the संगठन reports विश्वव्यापी membership of over 7.78 million adherents शामिल in इंजीलवाद, सम्मेलन उपस्थिति of over 12 million, और सालाना Memorial उपस्थिति of over 19 million.
They are निर्देशित by the शासी देह of यहोवा 's गवाह, a group of बड़ो in Brooklyn, New York, कि establishes all doctrines.
यहोवा 's गवाह ' मान्यताओं हैं आधारित on उनके interpretations of the Bible और वे prefer to उपयोग उनके अपना अनुवाद, the नई संसार अनुवाद of the पावन शास्त्रों.
They believe that the विनाश of the उपस्थित संसार प्रणाली at armageddon is imminent, and कि the स्थापना of God 's kingdom on earth is the तभी solution लिये सब समस्याएं faced by mankind.
The समूह उभरा from the बाइबल Student movement —founded in the लेट 1870s by Charles taze रसेल साथ the गठन of Zion 's देखें मीनार ट्रैक्ट Society —with significant organizational and doctrinal परिवर्तन अंतर्गत the नेतृत्व of जोसेफ फ्रैंकलिन रदरफोर्ड.
The नाम Jehovah 's गवाह, आधारित on यशायाह 43:10–12, थी अपनाया in 1931 to फर्क themselves from अन्य बाइबल Student groups और symbolize a ब्रेक साथ the legacy of Russell 's traditions.
यहोवा 's गवाह are best ज्ञात for उनके door-to-door उपदेश, distributing literature ऐसे as the Watchtower and जाग !
, and refusing सैन्य सेवा और रक्त transfusions.
वे consider use of the नाम Jehovah vital for उचित इबादत.
वे reject trinitarianism, अंतर्निहित अमरत्व of the आत्मा, और hellfire, which वे consider to be unscriptural doctrines.
वे do not observe Christmas, ईस्टर, जन्मदिन, or other holidays and कस्टम they consider to have pagan origins असंगत with christianity.
adherents commonly refer to उनके body of मान्यताओं as `` the सच्चाई '' और consider themselves to be `` in the सच्चाई ''.
वे consider धर्मनिरपेक्ष समाज to be morally भ्रष्ट और अंतर्गत the influence of Satan, and सबसे limit उनके सोशल interaction साथ non-witnesses.
Congregational disciplinary actions शामिल disfellowshipping, उनके term लिये औपचारिक expulsion और shunning.
baptized individuals जो formally छोड़ are माना disassociated and हैं also shunned.
Disfellowshipped और disassociated individuals may eventually be reinstated if deemed repentant.
the religion 's position regarding conscientious आपत्ति to सैन्य सेवा and refusal to सलाम national flags रै brought it into विरोध with some सरकारें.
Consequently, यहोवा 's Witnesses have been persecuted और उनके activities हैं banned or restricted in some देशों.
Persistent legal challenges by Jehovah 's Witnesses have बहकावे विधान सम्बन्धित to civil अधिकारों in अनेक countries.

Windows xp is an ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली produced by microsoft for use on personal कंप्यूटर, including घर और business desktops, लैपटॉप और media centers.
पहला released to computer निर्माताओं on अगस्त 24, 2001, it is the दूसरी सबसे popular संस्करण of Windows, based on संस्थापित user आधार.
the name `` xp '' is छोटी for `` अनुभव '', highlighting the उन्नत user अनुभव.
खिड़कियाँ XP, the successor to खिड़कियाँ 2000 और खिड़कियाँ me, थी the पहला consumer-oriented ऑपरेटिंग system produced by Microsoft to be built on the खिड़कियाँ nt kernel.
Windows xp थी released विश्वव्यापी for retail sale on अक्तूबर 25, 2001, और over 400 लाख copies यहूद in उपयोग in जनवरी 2006.
it थी succeeded by खिड़कियाँ Vista in जनवरी 2007.
Direct oem और retail बिक्री of Windows xp ceased on जून 30, 2008.
Microsoft जारी to sell Windows XP through उनके System Builders ( छोटी OEMs who sell समवेत computers ) कार्यक्रम जबतक January 31, 2009.
on April 10, 2012, microsoft reaffirmed कि विस्तारित support लिये Windows XP और दफ्तर 2003 would end on अप्रैल 8, 2014 और सुझाया that administrators शुरू preparing to migrate to a नए os.
the nt -आधारd संस्करण of खिड़कियाँ, which are प्रोग्रामित in C, C++, and सभा, हैं ज्ञात लिये उनके improved stability और efficiency over the 9x संस्करण of microsoft खिड़कियाँ.
खिड़कियाँ XP presented a significantly redesigned graphical उपयोक्ता interface, a बदलें microsoft promoted as अधिक user-friendly than पिछला संस्करण of Windows.
in an attempt to further ameliorate the `` dll hell `` कि plagued the पास्ट संस्करण of खिड़कियाँ, improved side-by-side assembly प्रौद्योगिकी in खिड़कियाँ XP allows side-by-side installation, पंजीकरण and servicing of अनेक संस्करण of globally साझा तन्त्र components in पूरा isolation.
it is also the पहला version of Windows to use उत्पाद सक्रियण to combat illegal copying.
During खिड़कियाँ xp 's विकास, the प्रोजेक्ट was codenamed `` Whistler '', after whistler, अंग्रेजों कोलंबिया, as अनेक microsoft कर्मचारी skied at the Whistler-Blackcomb ski रिज़ॉर्ट.
according to web analytics आंकड़ा generated by Net अनुप्रयोग, Windows xp was the सबसे widely प्रयुक्त ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली जबतक अगस्त 2012, when Windows 7 overtook it.
, खिड़कियाँ XP मार्केट share is at 38.99 %, having decreased almost every month चूंकि at least November 2007, the पहला माह लिये जिससे आंकडे are सरेआम उपलब्धियाँ इससे जाल Applications.
`` Por ऊना cabeza '' is an अर्जेंटाइन टैंगो with म्यूज़िक और lyrics written in 1935 by Carlos gardel and अल्फ्रेडो le प्रभा respectively.
the नाम is a स्पेनी horse-racing phrase meaning `` by a सिर '', जिससे refers to a घोड़ा जीतना a race by the लंबाई of एक सिर.
the गीत बोलो of a compulsive horse-track gambler जो compares उसके addiction लिये घोड़े साथ उसके attraction to महिलाओं.
अल्फ्रेडो Le प्रभा थी a Brazilian इससे São Paulo, a much italian-influenced area in Brazil, and भी the birthplace of zequinha de Abreu, composer of Tico-Tico no Fubá.
le Pera और gardel died in an वायुयान क्रैश in medellín, ( कोलंबिया ), on जून 24, 1935.

the baroreflex or baroreceptor reflex is एक of the देह 's homeostatic mechanisms लिये maintaining blood दबाव.
it provides a ऋणात्मक प्रतिक्रिया लूप in which an elevated रक्त दबाव reflexively causes दिल रेट to घटी इसलिए causing blood दबाव to घटी ; likewise, decreased रक्त pressure activates the baroreflex, causing दिल रेट to बढ़ाएँ यूँ causing an बढ़ाएँ in रक्त दबाव.
the system relies on specialized neurons, ज्ञात as baroreceptors, in the aortic arch, carotid साइनस, और elsewhere to monitor changes in रक्त दबाव and रिले them to the brainstem.
subsequent परिवर्तन in blood दबाव are mediated by the autonomic बेचैन system.
Atrial natriuretic पेप्टाइड forms a parallel ऋणात्मक प्रतिक्रिया loop in an endocrinological कंट्रास्ट to the renin-angiotensin प्रणाली.
the Loma prieta भूकंप, भी ज्ञात as the भूकंप of '89 and the संसार श्रेणी Earthquake, थी a प्रमुख earthquake कि struck the सैन Francisco खाड़ी क्षेत्रफल of कैलिफ़ोर्निया on अक्तूबर 17, 1989, at 5:04 pm लोकल समय.
caused by a स्लिप along the सैन andreas दोष, the quake lasted 10–15 सेकेंड और measured 6.9 on both the moment magnitude स्केल ( surface-wave परिमाण 7.1 ) और on the open-ended रिक्टर Scale.
the भूकंप मारे 63 लोगों throughout उत्तरी California, injured 3,757 and बाएँ कुछ 3,000–12,000 लोगों बेघर.
the earthquake occurred दौरान the warm-up अभ्यास for the तीसरा खेल of the 1989 संसार श्रेणी, featuring both of the Bay क्षेत्रफल 's Major League Baseball टीमों, the ओकलैंड एथलेटिक्स and the सैन Francisco दिग्गज.

साहूकार in the मानक Staunton पैटर्न
the साहूकार ( ♙♟ ) is the सबसे numerous और in सबसे हालातों the weakest piece in the game of chess, historically representing infantry or, अधिक विशेषकर, हथियारबंद peasants or pikemen.
in chess, प्रत्येक खिलाड़ी begins the खेल साथ eight pawns, एक on each वर्गाकार of the रैंक तत्काल in front of the अन्य टुकड़े.
( In बीजीय संकेतन, the white प्यादे start on a2, b2, c2,..., h2, while black pawns प्रारंभ on a7, b7, c7,..., h7. )
व्यक्तिगत प्यादे हैं referred to by the संचिका on which they स्टैंड.
लिये example, एक बोलती of `` श्वेत 's f-pawn '' or `` ब्लैक 's b-pawn '', or less commonly ( using वर्णनात्मक संकेतन ), `` White 's किंग 's bishop साहूकार '' or `` Black 's महारानी 's knight साहूकार ''.
It is भी common to refer to a rook साहूकार, अर्थ any pawn on the a- or h-file, a नाईट pawn ( on the b- or g-file ), a बिशप साहूकार ( on the c- or f-file ), a महारानी साहूकार ( on the d-file ), a king pawn ( on the e-file ), और a central साहूकार ( on either the d- or e-file ).
The सैन्य forces of the संसार have differing approaches to the enlistment of homosexual ( gay and lesbian ) और द्विलिंगी individuals.

Hydrogen उत्पादन is the परिवार of औद्योगिक विधि for generating hydrogen.
फिलहाल the प्रबल technology लिये direct उत्पादन is भाप reforming from hydrocarbons.
अनेक अन्य विधि हैं known including electrolysis और thermolysis.

5 लाख टन of हाइड्रोजन यहूद consumed on-site in आयल शोधन, and in the उत्पादन of ammonia ( haber process ) and methanol ( कटौती of कार्बन monoxide ).
0.4 लाख tonnes यहूद an incidental by-product of the chlor-alkali प्रक्रम.

a आधार point ( often denoted as bp, colloquially referred to in the बहुवचन as `` bips '', भी known as a `` बीप '' ) is a unit बराबर to one hundredth of a percentage point, or one भाग प्रति टेन हजार, 1/10000.
the वही unit is भी ( rarely ) called a permyriad, वस्तुतः अर्थ 'for ( every ) असंख्य ( टेन हजार ) ', और in that कॉन्टेक्स्ट is लिखा साथ जिससे looks जैसे a percent sign ( % ) with two अतिरिक्त zeroes at the समाप्त ( जैसे a stylized रूप of the four zeros in the denominator, हालांकि it originates as a natural extension of the प्रतिशत ( % ) और permille ( ‰ ) signs ).
a basis point is पारिभाषित as:
1 आधार point = 1 permyriad = एक one-hundredth percent
1 bp = 1 = 0.01 % = 0.1‰ = 10−4 = = 0.0001
1 % = 100 bp = 100
आधार points हैं used as a सुविधाजनक unit of measurement in contexts जहाँ प्रतिशत मतभेद of less than 1 % are discussed.
The सबसे आम उदाहरण is ब्याज दरों, जहाँ differences in interest दरों of कम than 1 % प्रति साल are प्रायः meaningful to talk about.
For example, a difference of 0.10 percentage अंक is समतुल्य to a change of 10 आधार अंक ( e.g. a 4.67 % रेट increases by 10 basis अंक to 4.77 % ).
Like प्रतिशत अंक, आधार points avoid the ambiguity between सापेक्ष and absolute discussions परिचय ब्याज rates by dealing only with the absolute change in numeric मान of a रेट.
लिये example, if a रपट says there रै महरूम a `` 1 % increase '' from a 10 % ब्याज rate, this could refer to an बढ़ाएँ either from 10 % to 10.1 % ( सापेक्ष, 1 % of 10 % ), or इससे 10 % to 11 % ( absolute, 1 % plus 10 % ).
if, however, the report says वहीँ रै महरूम a `` 10 basis पाइंट बढ़ाएँ '' from a 10 % interest रेट, then we जान कि the ब्याज rate of 10 % has increased by 0.10 % ( the absolute बदलें ) to a 10.1 % rate.
it is आम अभ्यास in the financial उद्योग to use basis अंक to denote a रेट बदलें in a वित्तीय यंत्र, or the अंतर ( स्प्रेड ) between दो ब्याज दरों, सहित the yields of fixed-income securities.
चूंकि certain लोन and bonds may commonly be कोटेड in संबंध to some अनुक्रमणिका or underlying सुरक्षा, वे होगा प्रायः be कोटेड as a spread over ( or अंतर्गत ) the index.
लिये उदाहरण, a ऋण कि bears interest of 0.50 % प्रति annum ऊपर the लंदन Interbank offered रेट ( LIBOR ) is कहा to be 50 basis अंक over libor, जिससे is commonly expressed as `` l+50bps '' or बस `` l+50 ''.
the पद `` basis point '' रै its origins in व्यापार the `` basis '' or the spread between दो interest rates.
चूंकि the आधार is प्रायः small, ये are quoted multiplied up by 10000, और hence a `` पूरा पाइंट '' गति in the `` basis '' is a basis पाइंट.
कंट्रास्ट with pips in fx forward markets.
the relationship between प्रतिशत changes और basis अंक can be summarized as फ़ॉलो : 1 percentage पाइंट बदलें = 100 आधार अंक, and 0.01 प्रतिशत अंक = 1 आधार पाइंट.
So, a बंध जिनकी yield increases from 5 % to 5.5 % is said to बढ़ाएँ by 50 आधार points ; or interest rates कि have risen 1 percentage पाइंट हैं said to have increased by 100 basis points.
The अंग्रेजों royal Family is the group of बंद रिश्तेदारों of the monarch of the संयुक्त Kingdom.
the term is भी commonly applied to the same group of लोगों जो हैं the संबंध of the monarch in her or उसके भूमिका as sovereign of any of the अन्य राष्ट्रमंडल realms, यूँ sometimes at variance साथ आधिकारिक national शर्तें for the family.
Members of the Royal Family belong to, either by जनम or marriage, the हाउस of विंडसर, चूंकि 1917, जब George V बदला the नाम of the royal हाउस from Saxe-Coburg और gotha.
This decision थी primarily लिया because ब्रिटेन और her साम्राज्य were at war साथ जर्मनी and दिए the British royal परिवार 's दमदार जर्मनी ancestry ; it थी felt कि इसके पब्लिक image could be improved by चुनना a more अंग्रेजों house name.
the new नाम चुनी, Windsor, had absolutely no कनेक्शन other than as the नाम of the castle which थी and continues to be a royal निवास.
हालांकि in the United किंगडम there is no strict विधिक or formal definition of who is or is नहीं a सदस्य of the royal परिवार, and different सूचियाँ will शामिल अलग लोगों, those carrying the style उसके or His majesty ( hm ), or Her or His royal Highness ( HRH ) are सदा माना सदस्यों, which प्रायः परिणाम in the अनुप्रयोग of the पद to the monarch, the consort of the monarch, the widowed consorts of पिछला monarchs, the children of the monarch और previous monarchs, the male-line grandchildren of the monarch and पिछला monarchs, और the spouses और the widows of a monarch 's and previous monarch 's sons and male-line पोते.

सदस्यों and relatives of the अंग्रेजों royal परिवार historically represented the monarch in विभिन्न स्थान throughout the अंग्रेजों साम्राज्य, sometimes लिये विस्तारित अवधि as viceroys, or लिये विशिष्ट ceremonies or कार्यक्रम.
Today, वे प्रायः perform ceremonial और social कर्तव्य throughout the संयुक्त किंगडम और विदेश on निमित्त of the संयुक्त Kingdom.
Aside from the monarch, उनके तभी संवैधानिक role in the अफेयर्स of सरकारी is to serve, if योग्य and जब नियुक्त by अक्षर patent, as a काउंसलर of राज्य, two or more of जिसको exercise the प्राधिकार of the क्राउन ( भीतर stipulated हद ) in the indisposal or absence from the अंग्रेजों फ्रेम of the monarch.
in the अन्य realms of the राष्ट्रमंडल रॉयल्टी do नहीं serve as counsellors of राज्य.
however in each ऐसे फ्रेम the monarch 's family सदस्यों may act on behalf of, हैं वित्तपोषित by, और represent the sovereign of that particular राज्य, और नहीं the United किंगडम.
The महारानी, उसके consort, उसके children और grandchildren, as खूब as सब पूर्व अधिपति ' children और grandchildren hold स्थान in the पहला sections of the आधिकारिक आदेश of precedence in इंग्लैण्ड और Wales, स्कॉटलैंड, और उत्तरी Ireland.
पत्नियां of the कहा enjoy their husbands ' पूर्वता, and पतियों of राजकुमारियों are unofficially लकिन habitually लगाई साथ उनके पत्नियां as well.

हैती ( ; haitian Creole ayiti ), officially the गणतंत्र of हैती ( ; ), is a Caribbean देश.
It occupies the पश्चिमी, छोटी portion of the island of हिस्पानिओला, in the वृहद Antillean archipelago, जिससे it साझा with the Dominican Republic.
ayiti ( जमीन of ऊँची kyu ) थी the indigenous taíno or amerindian नाम for the island.
the country 's highest पाइंट is Pic la Selle, at.
the कुल क्षेत्रफल of हैती is and इसके capital is port-au-prince.
haitian क्रियोल और French are the official भाषाएं.
Haiti 's क्षेत्रीय, ऐतिहासिक, और ethno-linguistic स्थिति is अद्वितीय लिये अनेक कारण.
It थी the first स्वतंत्र स्वदेश of Latin America and the Caribbean, the पहला ब्लैक -led republic in the संसार, और the दूसरी गणतंत्र in the americas जब it gained स्वतंत्रता in 1804 as भाग of a कामयाब slave revolution स्थायी nearly a decade.
in 2012, Haiti announced इसके intention to seek associate सदस्यता status in the African Union.
हैती is the most populous of the predominantly Francophone independent राष्ट्र in the americas.
it is एक of only दो स्वतंत्र nations in the Americas ( साथ साथ Canada ) to designate फ्रेंच as an official भाषा ; the अन्य french-speaking क्षेत्रों are all विदेशी départements, or collectivités, of France.
हैती is the सबसे populous पूरा member-state of the caribbean Community ( caricom ).
It is the poorest देश in the Americas as measured by the Human विकास अनुक्रमणिका.
राजनैतिक हिंसा has occurred regularly throughout इसके history, अग्रणी to government अस्थिरता.

michel Martelly, the वर्तमान अध्यक्ष, थी निर्वाचित in the haitian general चुनाव, 2011.
the island has था a इतिहास of destructive भूकंप.

The highest reliable मौत गिनती थी अनुमानित at 220,000.

The अध्यक्षीय राजमहल, पार्लियामेंट और many अन्य महत्वपूर्ण structures यहूद destroyed, साथ साथ अनगिनत homes and businesses, leaving सैंकड़ों of हज़ारों of लोगों homeless.
the देश has yet to recover from the 2010 earthquake ( and subsequent incidents ) due to दोनो the गंभीरता of the क्षति Haiti endured in 2010, as well as a सरकारी कि थी अप्रभावी खूब पहले the earthquake.

A पेजर is a बेतार दूरसंचार device that receives and प्रदर्शक numeric or text messages, or receives और announces आवाज़ संदेश.
one-way pagers can only receive messages, जबकि जवाब pagers and two-way pagers can भी acknowledge, जवाब to, and originate संदेश using an internal ट्रांसमीटर.
pagers operate as भाग of a paging प्रणाली जिससे शामिल one or more फिक्स्ड ट्रांसमीटरों ( or in the मामला of response pagers और two-way pagers, one or more आधार stations ), as well as a क्रमांक of pagers carried by mobile उपयोक्ता.
ये प्रणालियों can range from a restaurant system साथ a सिंगल low-power ट्रांसमीटर, to a देशभर प्रणाली साथ thousands of high-power base स्टेशन.
एक of the पहला व्यावहारिक paging सेवाएं was launched in 1950 लिये physicians in the नई York नगर क्षेत्रफल.
Physicians सशुल्क us $ 12 प्रति माह लिये the service और carried a ( 6 oz ) पेजर that would प्राप्त फोन संदेश भीतर ( 25 mi ) of a सिंगल ट्रांसमीटर मीनार.
The प्रणाली थी manufactured by the reevesound कम्पनी और संचालित by telanswerphone.
in 1960, John फ्रांसिस Mitchell संयुक्त elements of मोटोरोला 's walkie talkie और automobile रेडियो technologies to बनाएँ the first transistorized पेजर, and इससे इस point, paging प्रौद्योगिकी continued to advance, and पेजर adoption जारी to expand, जबतक the जल्दी 1990s.
however, by the mid-1990s, as cellular technologies became cheaper और more widely available, advanced services began to displace paging as a commercial उत्पाद.
Today, pagers exist largely as niche उत्पाद, ढूंढना preferential use in अनुप्रयोग such as अस्पताल, पब्लिक सुरक्षा, और retail locations जहाँ उनके सादगी, ऊँची विश्वसनीयता, और कम cost represent significant advantages.
Reevesville is a कस्बा in Dorchester County, दक्षिण Carolina, संयुक्त राज्य.
The जनसांख्यिकी was 196 at the 2010 जनसांख्यिकी.
as पारिभाषित by the u.S. दफ्तर of प्रबन्धन और बजट, और प्रयुक्त by the U.S. जनसांख्यिकी Bureau लिये सांख्यिकीय उद्देश्य तभी, reevesville is शामिल भीतर the charleston-north charleston-summerville metropolitan क्षेत्रफल.
Frida kahlo de Rivera ( born magdalena कार्मेन frieda kahlo y Calderón ; July 6, 1907 – जुलाई 13, 1954 ) was a Mexican चित्रकार, born in Coyoacán, जो is best ज्ञात लिये उसके self-portraits.
Kahlo 's जीवन began और ended in Mexico नगर, in her घर ज्ञात as the ब्लू हाउस.
वो दिया उसके जनम date as July 7, 1910, but उसके birth प्रमाणपत्र shows जुलाई 6, 1907.
kahlo had allegedly चाही the साल of her जनम to coincide साथ the साल of the शुरूआत of the Mexican revolution so that her life would शुरू साथ the birth of आधुनिक Mexico.
Her work रै been celebrated in मैक्सिको as emblematic of नेशनल और स्वदेशी परंपरा, और by नारीवादी for इसके uncompromising चित्रण of the मादा अनुभव और form.
मैक्सिकन संस्कृति और Amerindian सांस्कृतिक परंपरा हैं महत्वपूर्ण in her कार्य, which has been sometimes characterized as Naïve आर्ट or लोक आर्ट.
Her work रै also महरूम described as `` surrealist '', और in 1938 आंद्रे ब्रेटन, principal initiator of the surrealist गति, described kahlo 's आर्ट as a `` रिबन around a bomb ''.
kahlo had a volatile marriage with the प्रसिद्ध Mexican कलाकार डिएगो Rivera.
She suffered lifelong स्वास्थ्य समस्याएं.
Many of उसके health problems were the परिणाम of a ट्रैफ़िक दुर्घटना she बच as a किशोरावस्था.
recovering from उसके चोटों isolated उसके इससे other लोगों and इस isolation बहकावे her works, अनेक of जिससे हैं self-portraits of एक sort or another.
Kahlo सुझाया, `` I पेंट myself because I am so प्रायः alone और because I am the विषय I जान बेहतरीन. ''
वो भी stated, `` i was born a कुतिया.
I थी born a चित्रकार. ''

oktoberfest is a 16-day पर्व celebrating beer आयोजित annually in Munich, बायर्न, जर्मनी, running from late September to the first वीकेंड in अक्तूबर.
It is one of the most प्रसिद्ध events in Germany और is the संसार 's largest मेला, साथ अधिक than 6 million लोगों इससे around the world उपस्थित the इवेंट every साल.
to the स्थानीय, it is नहीं पुकारा Oktoberfest, but `` die wiesn '', बाद the colloquial नाम of the fairgrounds themselves.
the Oktoberfest is an महत्वपूर्ण भाग of Bavarian संस्कृति, having been held चूंकि 1810.
अन्य शहरों across the संसार भी hold Oktoberfest celebrations, modeled after the असली म्यूनिख इवेंट.
the म्यूनिख Oktoberfest originally took प्लेस दौरान the सोलह दिनों up to, and सहित, the first संडे in अक्तूबर.
In 1994, the schedule थी परिवर्धित in जवाब to जर्मनी reunification so that if the पहला संडे in October जलप्रपात on the 1st or 2nd, तब the festival होता go on जबतक October 3 ( जर्मनी एकता दिन ).
यूँ, the पर्व is अभी 17 दिनों जब the पहला संडे is अक्तूबर 2 और 18 दिनों जब it is अक्तूबर 1.
In 2010, the पर्व lasted until the first Monday in अक्तूबर, to चिह्नित the वर्षगांठ of the इवेंट.
the पर्व is आयोजित in an area नामित the Theresienwiese ( फ़ील्ड, or meadow, of Therese ), प्रायः called wiesn लिये short, स्तिथ near म्यूनिख 's center.
विशाल quantities of oktoberfest बियर are consumed, with लगभग 7 लाख liters परोसा दौरान the 16 दिन festival in 2007.
विज़िटर may भी enjoy a wide किस्में of traditional food such as Hendl ( मुर्गा ), schweinebraten ( रोस्ट पोर्क ), Schweinshaxe ( grilled हैम ओल ), steckerlfisch ( ग्रील्ड मछली on a स्टिक ), Würstl ( sausages ) साथ with Brezeln ( pretzel ), knödel ( आलू or ब्रैड dumplings ), Käsespätzle ( चीज noodles ), reiberdatschi ( आलू pancakes ), Sauerkraut or Rotkohl/Blaukraut ( red गोभी ) along साथ ऐसे bar delicacies as obatzda ( a spiced cheese-butter spread ) और Weisswurst ( a white sausage ).

Wheels of Gouda
चीज is a generic term लिये a विविध समूह of milk-based food products.
चीज is उत्पादित in wide-ranging जायका, बनावट, और फ़ॉर्म.
Cheese consists of proteins और fat इससे मिल्क, प्रायः the milk of गायों, भैंस, बकरियों, or शीप.
it is उत्पादित by जामन of the मिल्क प्रोटीन casein.
Typically, the मिल्क is acidified और जोड of the एंजाइम rennet कल्याणकारी जामन.
the solids हैं separated और pressed into फाइनल रूप.
Some cheeses have molds on the rind or throughout.
सबसे cheeses melt at cooking temperature.
सैंकड़ों of प्रकार of चीज from विभिन्न देशों are उत्पादित.
Their शैलियाँ, textures and flavors निर्भर on the origin of the milk ( including the एनिमल 's diet ), whether वे have been pasteurized, the butterfat सामग्री, the bacteria और मोल्ड, the processing, और वृद्धावस्था.
herbs, मसाले, or लकडी smoke may be प्रयुक्त as flavoring एजेंटों.
the पीला to रेड color of अनेक cheeses, such as रेड लीसेस्टर, is सामान्यतः formed from adding annatto.
लिये a few cheeses, the मिल्क is curdled by adding acids ऐसे as सिरका or नीबू रस.
Most cheeses are acidified to a lesser उपाधि by bacteria, जिससे फेरे milk sugars into लैक्टिक acid, तब the जोड of rennet completes the curdling.
शाकाहारी विकल्प to rennet हैं available ; सबसे हैं produced by fermentation of the कवक mucor miehei, but others have been निकाली इससे various प्रजाति of the cynara thistle family.
चीज is valued लिये इसके portability, long जीवन, और high सामग्री of मोटे, प्रोटीन, calcium, and phosphorus.
चीज is अधिक कॉम्पैक्ट और रै a longer शेल्फ life than मिल्क, although कैसा long a cheese होगा keep may depend on the type of चीज ; labels on पैकेट्स of चीज प्रायः अर्जी that a cheese should be खपत within three to five दिनों of opening.
generally बोलना, hard cheeses पिछला longer than नरम cheeses, ऐसे as Brie or बकरी 's milk cheese.
cheesemakers near a dairy प्रदेश may benefit from fresher, lower-priced मिल्क, और निम्नतर शिपिंग costs.
the long storage life of कुछ चीज, विशेषकर if it is encased in a protective rind, allows selling when markets are favorable.
अतिरिक्त संघटक may be added to some cheeses, such as ब्लैक मिर्च, लहसुन, chives or cranberries.
a विशेषज्ञ seller of चीज is sometimes ज्ञात as a cheesemonger.
to become an expert in this फ़ील्ड, like वाइन or cooking, requires some औपचारिक शिक्षा और सालो of चख and hands-on experience.
इस position is typically जिम्मेदार लिये all aspects of the चीज inventory ; selecting the चीज मेनू, खरीदना, receiving, storage, और ripening.
विधिक citation सिग्नल हैं a set of brief abbreviated phrases or words used to clarify the प्राधिकार or significance of a legal citation as it relates to a proposition.
Signals सहायता a रीडर जल्दी discern meaning or उपयोगिता of a particular सन्दर्भ जब the reference itself करता नहीं provide adequate information.
Most citation सिग्नल are लगाई in सामने of the citation to जिससे वे लागू.
For example, in the अनुच्छेद जब writing a विधिक argument, it is important to refer to primary sources.
to assist readers in locating these स्त्रोत, it is वांछनीय to use a मानकीकृत citation स्वरूप.
See generally हार्वर्ड Law Review Association, The bluebook : a वर्दी System of Citation ( 18th ed. 2005 ).
Note, however, कि some न्यायालयों may आवश्यकता कोई legal papers कि हैं सुपुर्द to उन्हें to conform to a अलग citation स्वरूप.
the सिग्नल is the phrase `` देखिए generally, '' which indicates कि the citation `` the bluebook : A वर्दी प्रणाली of citation ( 18th ed. 2005 ) '' provides general पृष्ठभूमि information on the टॉपिक.
Neil एल्डन आर्मस्ट्रांग ( अगस्त 5, 1930 – अगस्त 25, 2012 ) थी an अमरीकी astronaut और the पहला व्यक्ति to चलना on the Moon.
he थी भी an aerospace इंजीनियर, नवल aviator, परीक्षण पायलट, और विश्वविद्यालयों professor.
पहले बनने an astronaut, आर्मस्ट्रांग was an officer in the U.S. Navy and served in the कोरियाई War.
बाद the war, he earned उसके स्नातक 's degree at purdue विश्वविद्यालयों and परोसा as a परीक्षण पायलट at the नेशनल सलाहकार कमेटी लिये aeronautics high-speed उड़ान स्टेशन, अभी ज्ञात as the ड्राइडेन Flight शोध Center, जहाँ he logged over 900 फ़्लाइट.
He बाद समाप्त ग्रैजुएट अध्ययन at the विश्वविद्यालयों of दक्षिणी California.
A participant in the u.S. Air फ़ोर्स 's Man in Space soonest and X-20 dyna-soar इंसान spaceflight programs, आर्मस्ट्रांग joined the नासा Astronaut corps in 1962.
he बना his पहला space उड़ान, as कमांड pilot of Gemini 8, in 1966, becoming नासा 's first civilian astronaut to fly in स्पेस.
On इस मिशन, he performed the पहला docking of two spacecraft, with पायलट दाउद स्कॉट.
Armstrong 's दूसरी and पिछला spaceflight थी as मिशन कमांडर of the अपोलो 11 चंद्रमा लैंडिंग, in July 1969.
On इस मिशन, आर्मस्ट्रांग and बज़ Aldrin descended to the चंद्र surface और खर्च two और a half hours exploring, while Michael कॉलिन्स remained in चंद्र orbit in the कमांड मोड्यूल.
साथ साथ कॉलिन्स और एल्ड्रिन, आर्मस्ट्रांग थी awarded the Presidential पदक of स्वतंत्रता by President Richard Nixon ; in 1978, अध्यक्ष jimmy Carter presented Armstrong the congressional Space पदक of Honor in 1978 ; he and उसके पूर्व crewmates प्राप्त the congressional सुनहरा पदक in 2009.
आर्मस्ट्रांग died in सिनसिनाटी, Ohio, on August 25, 2012, at the आयु of 82, after complications इससे कोरोनरी artery बायपास सर्जरी.
सचिवालय ( March 30, 1970 – अक्तूबर 4, 1989 ) थी an अमरीकी thoroughbred racehorse कि in 1973 became the first u.s. ट्रिपल Crown चैंपियन in 25 years.
He नियत race records in सब तीन कार्यक्रम in the श्रेणी — the केंटकी डर्बी ( 1:59.4 ), the preakness Stakes ( 1:53 ), और the belmont stakes ( 2:24 ) — रिकॉर्ड कि still स्टैंड today.
He is माना to be एक of the greatest thoroughbreds of all समय.
In 1999, ईएसपीएन ranked Secretariat the 35th best खिलाड़ी of the 20th सदी, the उच्चतम ranking racehorse on the सूची url_http.
he क्रमित दूसरी behind man o ' युद्ध in The blood-horse 's सूची of the Top 100 U.S. Racehorses of the 20th Century.
सचिवालय थी sired by Bold Ruler out of somethingroyal, by Princequillo.
He थी foaled at The Meadow in कैरोलीन County, वर्जिनिया.
जैसे his प्रसिद्ध पूर्ववर्ती man o ' युद्ध, सचिवालय थी a विशाल chestnut colt और was दिए the वही उपनाम, `` Big रेड. ''
Secretariat 's grandsire, Nasrullah, is भी the great-great-grandsire of 1977 ट्रिपल क्राउन winner Seattle Slew.
स्वामित्व by पैनी chenery, he थी trained by Lucien Laurin and mainly ridden by Canadian jockey Ron turcotte, साथ with प्रशिक्षु jockey Paul फेलिसियानो ( पहला two दौड़ ), और दिग्गज Eddie मेपल ( last race ).
He raced in Chenery 's Meadow stable 's blue and श्वेत checkered रंगों and his groom थी एडी स्वेद.
Secretariat stood लगभग लम्बा, and weighed, with a 75-inch girth, in his racing प्रधान.
मैड्रिड (, ) is the पूंजी and largest नगर of स्पेन.
the population of the city is roughly 3.3 लाख और the संपूर्ण population of the Madrid metropolitan क्षेत्रफल is गणना to be around 6.5 million.
it is the third-largest city in the यूरोपीय संघ, बाद London और बर्लिन, और its महानगर area is the third-largest in the European Union after लंदन and पेरिस.
the नगर spans a कुल of.
the नगर is located on the Manzanares नदी in the केन्द्र of both the देश and the Community of मैड्रिड ( which comprises the नगर of Madrid, its conurbation and विस्तारित suburbs और villages ) ; this जातियाँ is bordered by the autonomous समुदायों of castile और león and Castile-La Mancha.
as the पूंजी नगर of स्पेन, सीट of government, and निवास of the Spanish monarch, Madrid is also the राजनैतिक, economic and सांस्कृतिक centre of स्पेन.
the वर्तमान महापौर is Ana botella इससे the People 's पार्टी ( pp ).
The मैड्रिड शहरी agglomeration रै the third-largest जीडीपी in the European संघ and its प्रभाव in politics, शिक्षा, entertainment, पर्यावरण, मीडिया, fashion, विज्ञान, संस्कृति, and the कला सब योगदान to its status as एक of the world 's प्रमुख वैश्विक शहरों.
due to its economic आउटपुट, high मानक of जीना, और market आकार, Madrid is माना the प्रमुख वित्तीय केन्द्र of दक्षिणी यूरोपीय and the Iberian Peninsula ; it hosts the सिर कार्यालयों of the विशाल majority of the प्रमुख स्पेनी कंपनियाँ, ऐसे as Telefónica, Iberia or repsol.
Madrid is the सबसे touristic नगर of Spain, the fourth-most touristic of the continent, और the seventh सबसे visited नगर in the संसार according to Forbes.
is the 10th सबसे livable city in the संसार according to Monocle पत्रिका, in इसके 2010 अनुक्रमणिका.
मैड्रिड also ranks among the 12 greenest यूरोपीय शहरों in 2010. < ref name= '' एचटीटीपी : //www.citymayors.com/environment/greenest-cities-europe.html '' > मैड्रिड is फिलहाल a Candidate City for the 2020 Summer Olympics.
Madrid घरों the headquarters of the संसार पर्यटन Organization ( WTO ), belonging to the संयुक्त Nations संगठन ( UN ), the segib, the Organization of ibero-american States ( oei ), और the Public ब्याज oversight फलक ( PIOB ).
it भी hosts प्रमुख अंतरराष्ट्रीय संस्थानों regulators of Spanish : the Standing कमेटी of the संघ of स्पेनी भाषा अकादमियों, मुख्यालय of the royal Spanish अकादमी ( rae ), the Cervantes Institute और the न्यास of तात्कालिक Spanish ( fundéu ).
मैड्रिड organizes fairs as fitur, आरको, SIMO TCI और the Cibeles मैड्रिड फ़ैशन सप्ताह.
While Madrid possesses a आधुनिक अवसंरचना, it रै preserved the dekh and feel of अनेक of इसके ऐतिहासिक neighbourhoods and गलियों.
इसके लैंडमार्क शामिल the royal राजमहल of Madrid ; the teatro Real ( royal थिएटर ) with its लौटी 1850 ओपेरा हाउस ; the Buen Retiro पार्क, संस्थापित in 1631 ; the 19th-century National पुस्तकालयों भवन ( founded in 1712 ) containing कुछ of स्पेन 's ऐतिहासिक अभिलेख ; a विशाल number of National संग्रहालय, and the Golden Triangle of Art, स्तिथ along the paseo डेल प्राडो और comprising तीन आर्ट संग्रहालय : Prado संग्रहालय, the museo nacional centro de arte reina sofía, a संग्रहालय of modern आर्ट, और the Thyssen-Bornemisza संग्रहालय, जिससे completes the shortcomings of the अन्य two संग्रहालय.
cibeles राजमहल और फव्वारा have become the स्मारक प्रतीक of the नगर.
the path of the Via appia और of the Via Appia traiana.
Remains of the appian रास्ता in Rome, निकट quarto miglio
Near रोम.
the Appian रास्ता ( लैटिन और इतालवी : via Appia ) थी one of the earliest और strategically सबसे important रोमन roads of the प्राचीन गणतंत्र.
It connected रोम to brindisi, apulia, in southeast इटली.
इसके importance is indicated by इसके आम name, अंकित by statius :
appia teritur रेजिना longarum viarum
`` the appian रास्ता is the queen of the long roads ''
The सड़क is named after appius claudius Caecus, the रोमन censor जो began और समाप्त the first खण्ड as a military सड़क to the दक्षिण in 312 bc during the Samnite युद्धों.
The Draupner wave, a सिंगल giant वेव measured on नई Year 's Day 1995, finally पुष्टि the अस्तित्व of freak waves, which था previously महरूम considered near-mythical
Rogue waves ( भी ज्ञात as freak लहरें, monster waves, कातिल लहरें, चरम waves, और असामान्य waves ) हैं relatively विशाल और spontaneous ocean surface लहरें कि occur दूर आउट at समुद्र, और are a threat even to विशाल जहाजों और ocean liners.
in oceanography, they हैं अधिक precisely पारिभाषित as लहरें whose ऊँचाई is अधिक than twice the significant वेव ऊँचाई ( SWH ), जिससे is itself पारिभाषित as the औसत of the largest third of waves in a वेव रिकार्ड.
Therefore rogue लहरें are not necessarily the biggest लहरें found at समुद्र ; वे are, बल्कि, surprisingly large waves लिये a दिए समुद्र state.
दुष्ट लहरें seem नहीं to have a single पृथक cause, but occur where शारीरिक कारकों such as high winds और दमदार currents cause लहरें to विलय to create a सिंगल exceptional large wave.
electress sophia of Hanover ( 1630–1714 )
The line of उत्तराधिकार to the British सिंहासन is the ordered अनुक्रम of सब those लोगों योग्य to succeed to the सिंहासन of the संयुक्त किंगडम and the other 15 Commonwealth realms.
The Act of उपनिवेश 1701 bestowed उत्तराधिकार on the Electress sophia of Hanover और her वंशजों while excluding रोमन Catholics.
the अंग्रेजों सरकारी does नहीं publish an official list of सब those in लकीर to सफल, but the कार्य of genealogical authors and amateur शोधकर्ताओं suggests कि वहीँ are several thousand people potentially in line.
At a summit in Perth, पश्चिमी ऑस्ट्रेलिया in 2011, the heads of सरकारी of all 16 राष्ट्रमंडल realms सहमत to लो steps to अपनाना निरपेक्ष primogeniture, end the exclusion of लोगों married to रोमन Catholics, और make अन्य परिवर्तन in the उत्तराधिकार नियम.

The युद्ध on आतंक ( भी ज्ञात as the वैश्विक War on Terrorism ) is a term commonly applied to an अंतरराष्ट्रीय military campaign जिससे प्रारंभ as a result of the 11 September 2001 terrorist attacks on the United States.
इस resulted in an international सैन्य अभियान to eliminate al-Qaeda और अन्य militant संगठन.
The संयुक्त Kingdom and अनेक other NATO और non-nato राष्ट्र participate in the विरोध.
the phrase 'War on आतंक ' was पहला प्रयुक्त by us President George W. बुश on 20 सितंबर 2001.
the बुश administration और the Western media have since प्रयुक्त the term to signify a global सैन्य, political, lawful, और conceptual struggle—targeting both organizations designated as terrorist और regimes अभियुक्त of supporting उन्हें.
It थी typically प्रयुक्त साथ a particular focus on उग्रवादी islamists, al-Qaeda, और अन्य जिहादी समूह.
Although the term is not officially used by the प्रशासन of US अध्यक्ष बराक ओबामा ( which instead uses the पद विदेशी आकस्मिकता आपरेशन ), it is स्टिल commonly used by राजनेता, in the मीडिया and by some aspects of government officially, ऐसे as the United राज्य ' वैश्विक War on आतंक Service पदक.

Blood दबाव ( BP ), sometimes referred to as arterial रक्त pressure, is the pressure exerted by circulating रक्त upon the walls of blood बरतन, and is one of the principal vital signs.
When प्रयुक्त without further specification, `` रक्त दबाव '' प्रायः refers to the arterial pressure of the प्रणालीगत परिसंचरण.
दौरान प्रत्येक heartbeat, रक्त pressure varies between a अधिकतम ( systolic ) और a न्यूनतम ( diastolic ) दबाव.
the रक्त दबाव in the circulation is प्रधानतया due to the pumping action of the heart.
Differences in औसत रक्त दबाव are responsible लिये blood प्रवाह इससे एक स्थान to another in the परिसंचरण.
the रेट of mean रक्त flow depends on the प्रतिरोध to flow presented by the रक्त बरतन.
औसत रक्त दबाव decreases as the circulating रक्त moves दूर इससे the heart through धमनियों और capillaries due to viscous नुकसान of उर्जा.
औसत blood दबाव बूंदें over the पूरे परिसंचरण, although most of the पतन occurs साथ the small arteries and arterioles.
गम्भीरता affects रक्त दबाव via hydrostatic forces ( e.g., दौरान standing ) और valves in veins, श्वास, and pumping from संकुचन of skeletal मांसपेशियां भी influence blood pressure in veins.
रक्त दबाव बगैर further specification प्रायः refers to the प्रणालीगत arterial दबाव measured at a व्यक्ति 's अपर भुजा और is a measure of the pressure in the brachial धमनी, the प्रमुख artery in the upper arm.
a person’s blood pressure is प्रायः expressed in शर्तें of the systolic दबाव over diastolic pressure और is measured in millimetres of mercury ( mmhg ), लिये example 120/80.
a veto – Latin for `` I forbid '' – is the शक्ति ( प्रयुक्त by an officer of the राज्य, for example ) to unilaterally stop an आधिकारिक कार्रवाई, विशेषकर the enactment of विधान.
a वीटो can be निरपेक्ष, as for instance in the संयुक्त राष्ट्र सुरक्षा Council, whose स्थाई members ( चीन, फ़्रांस, रूस, संयुक्त किंगडम, संयुक्त राज्य of America ) can ब्लाक कोई रेज़ोल्यूशन.
or it can be सीमित, as in the legislative प्रक्रम of the संयुक्त राज्य, where a two-thirds vote in दोनो the हाउस and सीनेट may ओवरराइड a अध्यक्षीय veto of legislation.
a वीटो only gives शक्ति to रोकें changes, नहीं to अपनाना उन्हें ( मगर for the विरल `` amendatory वीटो '' ).
यूँ a वीटो allows इसके होल्डर to protect the औकात quo.
the concept of a veto देह originated साथ the Roman consuls and tribunes.
Either of the two consuls पकड़कर दफ्तर in a दिए साल could block a military or सिविल निर्णय by the अन्य ; any ट्रिब्यून था the शक्ति to unilaterally ब्लाक विधान passed by the रोमन सीनेट.
गंधक डाइऑक्साइड ( भी गंधक डाइऑक्साइड ) is the रासायनिक यौगिक with the सूत्र.
it is a toxic गैस साथ a pungent, irritating smell, कि is released by volcanoes and in विभिन्न औद्योगिक processes.
चूंकि कोयले और petroleum प्रायः contain गंधक यौगिकों, उनके दहन generates गंधक dioxide जबतक the sulfur यौगिकों हैं removed पहले burning the fuel.
further oxidation of SO2, usually in the presence of a catalyst ऐसे as NO2, forms h2so4, and यूँ एसिड बरसात.
गंधक डाइऑक्साइड emissions are also a precursor to particulates in the atmosphere.
दोनो of these impacts are cause लिये चिंता over the पर्यावरणीय प्रभाव of ये fuels.
myasthenia gravis ( इससे Greek μύς `` मांसपेशी '', `` कमज़ोरी '', और `` गंभीर '' ; abbreviated MG ) is an असंक्राम्य neuromuscular disease leading to fluctuating muscle कमज़ोरी और fatigability.
it is an autoimmune विकार, in which weakness is caused by circulating antibodies that ब्लाक acetylcholine receptors at the postsynaptic neuromuscular जंक्शन, inhibiting the excitatory effects of the neurotransmitter acetylcholine on nicotinic receptors throughout neuromuscular junctions.
Myasthenia is treated medically with acetylcholinesterase inhibitors or immunosuppressants, और, in selected cases, thymectomy.
the disease incidence is 3–30 cases per million प्रति year and उठती as a result of increased awareness.
MG must be distinguished from जन्मजात myasthenic syndromes कि can present समान लक्षण लकिन प्रस्ताव no response to immunosuppressive उपचार.

A liquid-crystal display ( एलसीडी ) is a चपटा फलक प्रदर्शक, electronic विज़ुअल display, or video प्रदर्शक कि उपयोग the लाइट modulating properties of liquid crystals.
द्रव crystals do not emit light directly.
lcds हैं available to प्रदर्शक मनमानी बिंब ( as in a general-purpose कंप्यूटर प्रदर्शक ) or fixed images which can be प्रदर्शित or छुपा, ऐसे as preset शब्द, अंक, और 7-segment displays as in a डिजिटल क्लॉक.
They use the same basic प्रौद्योगिकी, मगर that मनमानी बिंब are made up of a विशाल number of छोटी pixels, while अन्य प्रदर्शक have larger तत्व.
LCDs हैं used in a wide range of applications including कंप्यूटर monitors, टेलीविज़न, यंत्र panels, वायुयान cockpit प्रदर्शक, and साइनेज.
They are आम in उपभोक्ता डिवाइस ऐसे as वीडियो players, गेमिंग डिवाइस, clocks, watches, calculators, and telephones, and have replaced कैथोड रे ट्यूब ( crt ) प्रदर्शक in most applications.
They हैं available in a wider दायरा of स्क्रीन sizes than crt and plasma प्रदर्शक, and चूंकि वे do not use phosphors, they do नहीं suffer image burn-in.
lcds are, however, susceptible to image persistence.
the एलसीडी स्क्रीन is अधिक energy कुशल और can be disposed of अधिक सकुशल than a crt.
इसके low electrical शक्ति खपत enables it to be used in बैटरी -powered इलेक्ट्रॉनिक equipment.
it is an electronically modulated optical यंत्र made up of कोई क्रमांक of segments filled साथ द्रव crystals और arrayed in सामने of a लाइट सोर्स ( backlight ) or reflector to उपज बिंब in रंग or monochrome.
द्रव crystals यहूद first खोजा in 1888.
by 2008, विश्वव्यापी बिक्री of टेलीविज़न with एलसीडी screens exceeded सालाना बिक्री of crt units ; the crt became obsolete लिये most उद्देश्य.

A बोतल of ऊँची potency b-complex विटामिन supplement गोलियां.
a विटामिन ( or ) is an सशुल्क यौगिक जरूरी by an organism as a vital nutrient in सीमित amounts.
an organic रासायनिक यौगिक ( or related नियत of compounds ) is पुकारा a विटामिन जब it can नहीं be synthesized in sufficient quantities by an organism, और must be प्राप्त from the diet.
Thus, the पद is सशर्त both on the हालातों and on the particular सजीव.
For उदाहरण, एस्कॉर्बिक acid ( विटामिन C ) is a विटामिन लिये humans, but नहीं लिये सबसे अन्य animals, and biotin and vitamin D are जरूरी in the इंसान आहार तभी in निश्चित हालातों.
By सम्मेलन, the पद विटामिन includes neither अन्य अनिवार्य nutrients, ऐसे as dietary खनिज, अनिवार्य fatty acids, or essential amino acids ( which हैं needed in larger amounts than विटामिन ) nor the large number of अन्य nutrients that प्रचार health लकिन are otherwise जरूरी less often.
तेरह विटामिन हैं universally पहचाना at उपस्थित.
Vitamins हैं classified by उनके biological और chemical activity, नहीं उनके ढांचा.
यूँ, each `` विटामिन '' refers to a क्रमांक of vitamer यौगिकों कि सब show the biological activity संबद्ध साथ a particular vitamin.
ऐसे a नियत of chemicals is grouped अंतर्गत an alphabetized विटामिन `` generic descriptor '' शीर्षक, ऐसे as `` विटामिन A ``, which शामिल the compounds retinal, रेटिनॉल, और four known carotenoids.
vitamers by definition हैं convertible to the क्रियाशील रूप of the विटामिन in the देह, और हैं sometimes inter-convertible to one another, as well.
Vitamins have diverse biochemical functions.
कुछ have hormone-like कृत्यों as regulators of mineral चयापचय ( ऐसे as vitamin d ), or regulators of cell और ऊतक growth और differentiation ( such as some फ़ॉर्म of vitamin a ).
अन्य फलन as antioxidants ( e.g., vitamin E और sometimes विटामिन C ).
The largest क्रमांक of विटामिन ( ऐसे as B complex vitamins ) फलन as precursors लिये enzyme cofactors, that सहायता एंजाइमों in उनके कार्य as catalysts in चयापचय.
in this भूमिका, vitamins may be tightly बंधी to enzymes as भाग of prosthetic समूह : For उदाहरण, biotin is भाग of एंजाइमों शामिल in बनाना वसीय acids.
Vitamins may भी be कम tightly बंधी to एंजाइम catalysts as coenzymes, detachable अणुओं कि function to carry रासायनिक groups or electrons between अणुओं.
For example, फोलिक एसिड may carry मिथाइल, formyl, और methylene groups in the कोशिका.
Although these roles in assisting enzyme-substrate reactions are विटामिन ' best-known function, the अन्य विटामिन कृत्यों हैं बराबर important.
जबतक the mid-1930s, जब the first commercial yeast-extract vitamin B complex और semi-synthetic विटामिन c supplement टैबलेट यहूद sold, विटामिन यहूद obtained solely through food सेवन, और परिवर्तन in diet ( जिससे, लिये उदाहरण, could occur दौरान a particular growing ऋतु ) प्रायः greatly altered the प्रकार और amounts of विटामिन ingested.
however, विटामिन have been उत्पादित as कमोडिटी रसायन और बना widely available as inexpensive semisynthetic और synthetic-source multivitamin dietary और food supplements and एडिटिव, since the middle of the 20th century.
संसार मुस्लिम population by percentage ( pew शोध Center, 2009 )
World Muslim जनसांख्यिकी in लाखो
islam is the world 's दूसरी largest धर्म बाद christianity.
According to a 2010 study, islam has 1.62 billion adherents, बनाना up over 23 % of the संसार जनसांख्यिकी.
islam is the predominant धर्म in the मध्य East, in Sahel, in the सींग of अफ़्रीकी and northern अफ़्रीकी, and in some भाग of Asia.
विशाल communities of मुसलमान हैं भी found in चीन, the Balkans, और Russia.
Other भाग of the world host large Muslim अप्रवासी communities ; in पश्चिमी यूरोपीय, लिये instance, islam is the second largest धर्म after christianity, जहाँ it represents 6 % of the कुल population.
according to the Pew Research बीच in 2010 there यहूद 49 Muslim-majority देशों.
around 62 % of the संसार 's मुसलमान सजीव in दक्षिण and southeast एशिया, with over 1 billion adherents.
The largest Muslim देश is इंडोनेशिया, घर to 12.7 % of the world 's मुसलमान, followed by Pakistan ( 11.0 % ), इण्डिया ( 10.9 % ), और बांग्लादेश ( 9.2 % ).
About 20 % of मुसलमान live in अरब देशों.
in the मध्य ईस्ट, the non-arab देशों of तुर्कों और Iran हैं the largest Muslim-majority countries ; in अफ़्रीकी, मिश्र और Nigeria have the सबसे populous मुस्लिम समुदायों.
a पढ़ाई conducted by the pew शोध बीच in 2010 और released जनवरी 2011 मिला that there हैं 1.62 अरब Muslims around the world.
the पढ़ाई मिला more Muslims in the संयुक्त किंगडम than in लेबनान and अधिक in चीन than in सीरियाई.
rhode Island ( or ), officially the State of rhode द्वीप और Providence बागानों, is a state in the New इंग्लैण्ड region of the United राज्य.
Rhode द्वीप is the smallest in area, the आठवीं least populous, लकिन the दूसरी सबसे densely populated of the 50 us states behind नई जर्सी.
Rhode द्वीप is bordered by Connecticut to the वेस्ट और मैसाचुसेट्स to the उत्तर और ईस्ट, और it साझा a water boundary साथ नई York 's Long Island to the southwest.
rhode द्वीप थी the पहला of the 13 असली colonies to घोषित स्वतंत्रता from British नियम, declaring itself स्वतंत्र on may 4, 1776, two months पहले कोई other उपनिवेश.
the State was भी the last of the thirteen असली colonies to ratify the United राज्य Constitution.
rhode द्वीप 's आधिकारिक nickname is `` the Ocean State '', a reference to the State 's geography, चूंकि rhode द्वीप रै several large bays and inlets कि राशि to about 14 % of इसके total area.
इसके जमीन area is, लकिन इसके कुल क्षेत्रफल is significantly larger.
Dubai ( ; ', ) is a city in the संयुक्त अरब अमीरात, located भीतर the अमीर of the वही name.
the emirate of Dubai is स्तिथ on the southeast coast of the पारसी Gulf on the arabian प्रायद्वीप and is एक of the सात अमीरात कि make up the देश.
it has the largest जनसांख्यिकी in the uae ( 2,106,177 ) और the second-largest जमीन territory by क्षेत्रफल ( 4,114 km2 ) बाद Abu धाबी.
Dubai और abu धाबी, the नेशनल पूंजी, are the तभी two emirates to have वीटो power over critical matters of national महत्व in the country 's विधानमंडल.
the नगर of दुबई is स्तिथ on the emirate 's northern तटरेखा और heads up the Dubai-Sharjah-Ajman महानगर area.
दुबई is आजकल often misperceived as a देश or city-state और, in कुछ cases, the uae as a पूरे has महरूम वर्णित as 'dubai '.
the earliest जिक्र of Dubai is in 1095 AD, and the earliest recorded उपनिवेश in the प्रदेश dates from 1799.
the Sheikhdom of दुबई थी formally established in 1833 by Sheikh Maktoum bin Butti Al-Maktoum जब he persuaded around 800 सदस्यों of उसके tribe of the Bani Yas, जीना in कया was तब the दूसरी सऊदी State और अभी भाग of सऊदी Arabia, to follow उसे to the Dubai Creek by the Abu Falasa गोत्र of the bani Yas.
it remained अंतर्गत the जनजाति 's कंट्रोल जब the United किंगडम assumed protection of the Sheikhdom in 1892 and joined the nascent संयुक्त अरब अमीरात upon स्वतंत्रता in 1971 as the देश 's second emirate.
Its strategic भौगोलिक स्थान made the कस्बा an महत्वपूर्ण व्यापार hub and by the शुरूआत of the 20th सदी, दुबई was already an important regional port.
आज, दुबई has उभरा as a कॉस्मोपॉलिटन metropolis कि has grown steadily to become a वैश्विक नगर और a कारोबार और सांस्कृतिक hub of the Middle ईस्ट और the पारसी गल्फ region.
हालांकि दुबई 's economy थी historically निर्मित on the आयल industry, the emirate 's Western-style मॉडल of कारोबार ड्राइव इसके अर्थव्यवस्था साथ the प्रमुख revenues अभी coming from पर्यटन, रियल एस्टेट, और वित्तीय सेवाएं.
दुबई रै recently attracted world attention through अनेक अभिनव large निर्माण प्रोजेक्ट and खेल events.
The नगर रै become symbolic for इसके skyscrapers और high-rise buildings, ऐसे as the world 's tallest burj खलीफा, in addition to ambitious development projects सहित man-made आइलैंड्स, hotels, and some of the largest खरीदारी malls in the प्रदेश और the world.
इस increased attention रै भी highlighted labor and human rights issues concerning the नगर 's largely South एशियाई सशुल्क workforce.
Dubai 's प्रॉपर्टी market अनुभवी a प्रमुख deterioration in 2008–2009 as a परिणाम of the विश्वव्यापी economic downturn following the financial crisis of 2007-2008.
however, Dubai has बना a स्थिर और क्रमिक रिकवरी with सहायता coming इससे neighboring अमीरात.
the handful of नई प्रोजेक्ट कि are in the पाइपलाइन have महरूम समर्थ to सहायता दुबई रियल estate make a comeback.
as of 2012, Dubai is the 22nd most महंगी city in the संसार, और the सबसे expensive city in the Middle ईस्ट, surpassing इसराईल 's Tel aviv ( 31st ).
Dubai has also been रेटेड as one of the बेहतरीन स्थान to सजीव in the Middle East, सहित by us American वैश्विक consulting firm मर्सर जो रेटेड the नगर as the best place to live in the मध्य ईस्ट in 2011.

an समंदर ( ; the संसार समंदर of शास्त्रीय antiquity ) is a देह of saline water that composes a large part of a planet 's hydrosphere.
in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of धरती, it refers to एक or all of the major divisions of the ग्रह 's संसार समंदर – वे हैं, in descending order of क्षेत्रफल, the Pacific, अटलांटिक, भारतीय, दक्षिणी ( Antarctic ), और आर्कटिक महासागर.
the शब्द `` समुद्र `` is often used interchangeably with `` समंदर '', but strictly बोलना a sea is a देह of saline जल ( possibly a division of the संसार Ocean ) partly or fully enclosed by land.
धरती is the तभी ग्रह known to have an ocean ( or any विशाल amounts of खोलें द्रव water ).
Approximately 72 % of the ग्रह 's सतह ( ~3.6x108 km2 ) is covered by saline water that is customarily विभाजित into अनेक principal महासागर और छोटी समंदर, साथ the ocean covering लगभग 71 % of the धरती 's सतह.
in terms of the जलमंडल of the Earth, the समंदर contains 97 % of the धरती 's water.
Oceanographers have stated कि आउट of 97 %, only 5 % of the समंदर as a पूरे on धरती रै महरूम explored.
क्युकी it is the प्रिंसिपल घटक of Earth 's hydrosphere, the संसार समंदर is अभिन्न to सब ज्ञात life, फ़ॉर्म भाग of the कार्बन साईकिल, and influences जलवायु और weather पैटर्न.
the कुल आवाज़ is लगभग 1.3 billion घन kilometres ( 310 million cu mi ) साथ an औसत गहराई of.
it is the habitat of 230,000 ज्ञात species, हालांकि much of the ocean 's depths remain unexplored and it is अनुमानित that over two लाख समुद्री प्रजाति मौजूद.
the origin of धरती 's महासागर is still unknown, लकिन oceans are believed to have formed in the hadean period and may have महरूम the impetus for the emergence of life.
extraterrestrial oceans may be composed of a चौड़ी range of तत्व and यौगिकों.
the only पुष्टि विशाल stable लाशें of extraterrestrial surface liquids हैं the झीलों of Titan, although there is evidence लिये the existence of oceans elsewhere in the Solar प्रणाली.
जल्दी in their भूगर्भिक histories, मंगल और शुक्र हैं theorized to have था विशाल जल महासागर.
the Mars समंदर hypothesis suggests कि nearly a तीसरा of the सतह of मंगल थी एकबार covered by जल, though the जल on Mars is no longer oceanic, और a runaway ग्रीनहाउस प्रभाव may have boiled दूर the global समंदर of Venus.
यौगिकों such as salts और अमोनिया dissolved in जल निम्नतर इसके जमने पाइंट, so कि जल might मौजूद in विशाल quantities in extraterrestrial environments as brine or convecting बर्फ.
Unconfirmed महासागर are speculated beneath the सतह of many बौना planets और natural satellites ; notably, the समंदर of यूरोपा is believed to have over twice the जल volume of धरती.
the सौर प्रणाली 's गैस दानव planets हैं भी believed to possess liquid वायुमंडलीय layers of yet to be पुष्टि रचनाएं.
Oceans may भी मौजूद on exoplanets and exomoons, सहित surface महासागर of द्रव जल भीतर a परितारकीय habitable मण्डल.
समंदर planets हैं a काल्पनिक type of ग्रह with a सतह completely covered साथ द्रव.
एल्विस आरोन Presley ( जनवरी 8, 1935 – August 16, 1977 ) थी an American singer और actor.
a सांस्कृतिक icon, he is commonly ज्ञात by the सिंगल नाम Elvis.
One of the सबसे popular musicians of the 20th सदी, he is प्रायः referred to as the `` किंग of चट्टान and फेंकें '' or `` the किंग ''.
born in Tupelo, मिसिसिपी, प्रेस्ली स्थानांतरित to Memphis, टेनेसी, with उसके परिवार at the आयु of 13.
He began उसके करियर there in 1954, working साथ सूर्य रिकॉर्ड owner Sam Phillips, जो wanted to लाओ the ध्वनि of African-American म्यूज़िक to a wider audience.
accompanied by guitarist Scotty मूर and bassist विधेयक Black, प्रेस्ली was the सबसे important popularizer of rockabilly, an uptempo, backbeat -ड्राइवn संलयन of देश and लय and blues.
आरसीए Victor acquired उसके contract in a सौदे arranged by कर्नल tom पार्कर, जो went on to मैनेज the singer for over दो दशकों.
प्रेस्ली 's पहला आरसीए सिंगल, `` heartbreak Hotel ``, released in जनवरी 1956, थी a number-one hit.
he became the अग्रणी figure of the newly लोकप्रिय sound of चट्टान और फेंकें साथ a श्रेणी of संजाल television appearances और chart-topping रिकॉर्ड.
उसके energized interpretations of songs, अनेक इससे African-American स्त्रोत, and his uninhibited प्रदर्शन style बना him enormously popular—and controversial.
In नवम्बर 1956, he बना उसके film debut in प्रेम Me Tender.
drafted into सैन्य service in 1958, प्रेस्ली relaunched उसके recording करियर two सालो बाद साथ some of his सबसे commercially successful कार्य.
he staged few कॉन्सर्ट however, and हिदायत by पार्कर, proceeded to devote much of the 1960s to बनाना हॉलीवुड फिल्मों and soundtrack albums, सबसे of them critically derided.
in 1968, बाद सात years away from the stage, he लौटे to सजीव performance in a celebrated वापसी टेलीविज़न खास कि led to an extended लास Vegas कॉन्सर्ट रेसिडेंसी और a स्ट्रिंग of लाभप्रद टुर.
in 1973 Presley मंचन the पहला कॉन्सर्ट ब्रॉडकास्ट globally via उपग्रह, aloha from हवाई.
नुस्खा ड्रग abuse severely deteriorated his स्वास्थ्य, और he died एकाएक in 1977 at the age of 42.
प्रेस्ली is regarded as one of the सबसे important figures of 20th-century popular संस्कृति.
He had a versatile voice और unusually wide कामयाबी encompassing many जाति, सहित country, पॉप ballads, gospel, and ब्लूज़.
he is the best-selling सोलो artist in the history of popular म्यूज़िक.
मनोनीत लिये 14 competitive Grammys, he जीती three, and प्राप्त the ग्रैमी Lifetime उपलब्धि पुरस्कार at आयु 36.
he रै been inducted into अनेक म्यूज़िक हॉल of fame.
A glass of रूट बियर साथ झाग
रूट बियर is a carbonated, sweetened पेय, originally made using the root of a sassafras plant ( or the छाल of a sassafras tree ) as the प्राथमिक स्वाद.
रूट बियर, popularized in North अमेरिका, आता in दो फ़ॉर्म : alcoholic और soft पेय.
the historical रूट beer was analogous to छोटी बियर in कि the प्रक्रम provided a पेय with a बहुत low दारू content.
हालांकि जड़ें हैं प्रयुक्त as the source of अनेक नरम पेय throughout the world, प्रायः अलग names are used.
fluorescent खनिज emit दृश्य लाइट जब उजागर to ultraviolet लाइट
Fluorescence is the उत्सर्जन of लाइट by a पदार्थ कि रै absorbed लाइट or अन्य इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक विकिरण.
it is a रूप of luminescence.
in सबसे cases, the उत्सर्जित लाइट has a longer wavelength, और इसलिए निम्नतर energy, than the अवशोषित radiation.
however, जब the अवशोषित इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक radiation is तीव्र, it is संभावित लिये one इलेक्ट्रॉन to अवशोषित दो photons ; इस two-photon absorption can सीसे to उत्सर्जन of radiation having a shorter wavelength than the अवशोषित विकिरण.
The उत्सर्जित विकिरण may भी be of the वही wavelength as the अवशोषित विकिरण, termed `` अनुनाद fluorescence ''.
the most striking उदाहरण of fluorescence occur when the अवशोषित radiation is in the पराबैंगनी region of the spectrum, and यूँ invisible to the इंसान eye, और the emitted light is in the दृश्य प्रदेश.
प्रतिदीप्ति रै अनेक practical अनुप्रयोग, including mineralogy, gemology, chemical सेंसर ( fluorescence spectroscopy ), fluorescent लेबलिंग, dyes, biological डिटेक्टरों, and, सबसे commonly, fluorescent दीये.
अनौपचारिक logic, intuitively, refers to the principles of लॉजिक और लॉजिकल विचार outside of a औपचारिक setting.
however, शायद क्युकी of the अनौपचारिक in the title, the precise परिभाषा of अनौपचारिक लॉजिक is a matter of some विवाद.
ralph H. जॉनसन और J. एंथोनी ब्लेयर define अनौपचारिक logic as `` a शाखा of लॉजिक whose कार्य is to develop non-formal standards, मापदण्ड, प्रक्रियाओं लिये the विश्लेषण, interpretation, evaluation, आलोचना and निर्माण of argumentation. ''
इस परिभाषा reflects कया had महरूम अव्यक्त in their अभ्यास और what अन्य were doing in उनके अनौपचारिक लॉजिक ग्रन्थ.
अनौपचारिक logic is associated साथ ( अनौपचारिक ) fallacies, critical सोच, the Thinking कौशल गति और the interdisciplinary inquiry ज्ञात as argumentation सिद्धान्त.
Frans H. वैन Eemeren writes that the लेबल `` informal लॉजिक '' कवर a `` संग्रहण of normative approaches to the study of तर्क in ordinary भाषा कि remain करीब to the अभ्यास of argumentation than formal logic. ''
