the Great Depression began in August of 1929, जब the United राज्य economy पहला गई into an economic recession.
Although the देश खर्च दो महीने साथ declining जीडीपी, it was not until the वॉल Street क्रैश of अक्तूबर, 1929 that the effects of a declining अर्थव्यवस्था were लगा, और a major worldwide economic downturn ensued.
the मार्केट crash marked the beginning of a दशक of high बेरोजगारी, गरीबी, कम profits, अपस्फीति, plunging फार्म incomes, और खोया opportunities for economic विकास और निजी उन्नति.
हालांकि इसके कल्याणकारी are स्टिल uncertain and विवादास्पद, the net effect was a अचानक और सामान्य loss of विश्वास in the आर्थिक भविष्य.
the usual स्पष्टीकरण शामिल numerous कारकों, विशेषकर high उपभोक्ता debt, ill-regulated markets that permitted overoptimistic लोन by banks and निवेशकों, और the कमी of high-growth नई industries, all interacting to बनाएँ a downward economic spiral of reduced बिता, falling confidence, और lowered उत्पादन.
Industries कि suffered the most शामिल construction, कृषि as dust-bowl conditions persisted in the agricultural heartland, शिपिंग, खनन, और लॉगिंग as खूब as टिकाऊ goods जैसे ऑटोमोबाइल और appliances that could be postponed.
the economy reached नीचे in the शीत of 1932–33 ; then came four सालो of बहुत रैपिड विकास जबतक 1937, when the मंदी of 1937 brought वापस 1934 स्तर of बेरोजगारी.
the अवसाद caused प्रमुख political परिवर्तन in America.
तीन years into the depression, हर्बर्ट Hoover खोया the 1932 presidential चुनाव to फ्रैंकलिन delano रूज़वेल्ट in a sweeping भूस्खलन.
रूज़वेल्ट 's आर्थिक recovery योजना, the नई सौदे, instituted unprecedented कार्यक्रम लिये relief, रिकवरी और सुधार, और brought परिचय a प्रमुख realignment of अमरीकी राजनीती.
The अवसाद भी resulted in an increase of करणों of लोगों to अन्य countries लिये the first time in American history.
For उदाहरण, कुछ immigrants went back to उनके native countries, and some native US नागरिकों गई to कनाडा, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, और दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी.
It भी resulted in the mass माइग्रेशन of people इससे badly hit areas in the ग्रेट मैदान and the South to places ऐसे as कैलिफ़ोर्निया और the उत्तर, respectively ( देखिए okies and the Great Migration of अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी ).
Racial तनाव भी increased दौरान इस time.
by the 1940s immigration था लौटे back to सामान्य, और करणों अस्वीकृत.
A well-known उदाहरण of an emigrant थी फ़्रैंक McCourt, जो went to आयरलैंड, as recounted in his किताब एंजेला 's राख.
the मेमोरी of the Depression also shaped आधुनिक theories of economics and resulted in अनेक परिवर्तन in कैसा the सरकारी dealt with economic downturns, ऐसे as the उपयोग of stimulus पैकेज, keynesian economics, और सोशल सुरक्षा.
it भी shaped आधुनिक American साहित्य, resulting in famous novels ऐसे as जॉन steinbeck 's `` the अंगूर of प्रकोप `` और `` of चूहे and Men ``.
The Great Depression of the 1930s प्रारंभ साथ the stock मार्केट क्रैश of अक्तूबर 1929.
तुर्कों ( ), officially the गणतंत्र of तुर्कों, is a transcontinental country, स्तिथ ज़्यादातर on आनातोलिया in पश्चिमी एशिया और on ईस्ट Thrace in southeastern यूरोपीय.
तुर्कों is bordered by आठ countries : बुल्गारिया to the उत्तरपश्चिम ; Greece to the वेस्ट ; जॉर्जिया to the पूर्वोत्तर ; Armenia, इरान और the Azerbaijani exclave of Nakhchivan to the ईस्ट ; और Iraq and सीरियाई to the southeast.
The Mediterranean Sea is to the दक्षिण ; the ईजियन समुद्र is to the west ; और the Black Sea is to the उत्तर.
the समुद्र of मरमरा, the Bosphorus and the Dardanelles ( जिससे together रूप the तुर्की straits ) demarcate the boundary between thrace और आनातोलिया ; they भी पृथक Europe and एशिया.
Turkey 's स्थान at the क्रॉसरोड्स of यूरोपीय और एशिया makes it a देश of significant geostrategic महत्व.
the देश 's आधिकारिक भाषा is तुर्की, a turkic भाषा, जिससे is spoken by लगभग 85 % of the जनसांख्यिकी as माँ जीभ.
the most numerous जातीय समूह is the turks, जो constitute between 70 % और 75 % of the population according to the World factbook.
kurds हैं the largest जातीय अल्पसंख्यक और, according to the वही source, क्रमांक around 18 % of the population जबकि अन्य जातीय अल्पसंख्यकों are estimated to be at 7–12 %.
the vast majority of the जनसांख्यिकी is Muslim.
the area अभी पुकारा तुर्कों रै been inhabited since the paleolithic, सहित विभिन्न प्राचीन Anatolian सभ्यताओं और thracian peoples.
After Alexander the ग्रेट 's conquest, the area थी hellenized, which जारी साथ the Roman नियम and the परिवर्तन into the Byzantine साम्राज्य.
The सलजूक़ turks began migrating into the क्षेत्रफल in the 11th सदी, starting the प्रक्रम of Turkification, जिससे थी greatly त्वरित by the सलजूक़ विजय over the Byzantines at the बैटल of manzikert in 1071.
the Seljuk सल्तनत of rûm ruled आनातोलिया जबतक the Mongol invasion in 1243, upon जिससे it disintegrated into अनेक small तुर्की beyliks.
Starting from the लेट 13th सदी, the Ottoman beylik संयुक्त आनातोलिया और created an साम्राज्य encompassing much of southeastern Europe, पश्चिमी एशिया और उत्तर अफ़्रीकी.
After the Ottoman साम्राज्य collapsed following इसके शिकस्त in संसार युद्ध i, parts of it were occupied by the विजयी allies.
A cadre of यंग military अधिकारियों, led by mustafa kemal अतातुर्क और his सहयोगियों, व्यवस्थित a कामयाब resistance to the allies ; in 1923 वे स्थापित the आधुनिक गणतंत्र of तुर्कों, साथ अतातुर्क as इसके first अध्यक्ष.
तुर्कों is a democratic, धर्मनिरपेक्ष, unitary, संवैधानिक गणतंत्र with a diverse cultural heritage.
तुर्कों has become increasingly एकीकृत with the वेस्ट through सदस्यता in संगठनों ऐसे as the परिषद of Europe, नाटो, oecd, osce और the g-20 major economies.
Turkey began full membership negotiations साथ the European संघ in 2005, having महरूम an संबद्ध सदस्य of the European Economic जातियाँ चूंकि 1963 और having joined the eu Customs संघ in 1995.
Turkey रै भी fostered बंद cultural, political and आर्थिक संबंध with the मध्य ईस्ट, Caucasus, the Turkic राज्य of Central Asia and the अफ़्रीकी countries through membership in संगठनों such as the Turkic Council, संयुक्त प्रशासन of Turkic कला और संस्कृति, संगठन of इस्लामी Cooperation and the आर्थिक सहयोग संगठन.
तुर्कों 's growing economy and diplomatic पहलों have led to its recognition as a regional शक्ति.
तुर्कों is the संसार 's 17th largest अर्थव्यवस्था by नाममात्र GDP और the 16th largest by खरीदना शक्ति parity.
Caryn Elaine जॉनसन, best known as whoopi Goldberg (, ( born नवम्बर 13, 1955 ) is an अमरीकी comedienne, अभिनेत्री, singer-songwriter, राजनैतिक activist, लेखक और talk दिखाएँ मेजबान.
Goldberg made उसके फिल्मी डेब्यू in The रंग Purple ( 1985 ), playing celie, a mistreated black स्त्री in the Deep South.
She प्राप्त a नामांकन for the अकादमी Award for बेहतरीन अभिनेत्री and जीती उसके first सुनहरी ग्लोब Award लिये उसके भूमिका in the film.
in 1990, वो played oda mae भूरा, a wacky मानसिक helping a slain man ( पैट्रिक swayze ) सहेजें उसके lover ( Demi मूर ) in the ब्लॉकबस्टर Ghost.
This प्रदर्शन जीती उसके a दूसरी Golden ग्लोब and an Academy Award लिये बेहतरीन Supporting Actress ; इस made Goldberg only the दूसरी black स्त्री in the history of the अकादमी पुरस्कार to win an एक्टिंग oscar—the पहला being हैटी McDaniel जो जीती लिये Gone साथ the Wind in 1939.
Notable later films include Sister Act and सिस्टर अधिनियम 2, The Player, बना in America, कैसा स्टेला मिला उसके नाली वापस, Girl, बाधित और Rat रेस.
वो is भी acclaimed लिये her roles as the बारटेंडर guinan in स्टार Trek : the Next Generation, as टेरी doolittle in jumpin ' जोकर फ्लैश, and as कार्मेन Tibideaux in ग्ली, as well as the voice of shenzi the लकड़बग्घा in the शेर किंग.
गोल्डबर्ग रै been मनोनीत लिये 13 एमी Awards लिये उसके work in television.
She थी co-producer of the लोकप्रिय game show हॉलीवुड वर्गों इससे 1998 to 2004.
वो has महरूम the मॉडरेटर of the दिन बात दिखाएँ the View चूंकि 2007.
Goldberg has a ग्रैमी, दो दिन emmys, two सुनहरी ग्लोब्स, a Tony ( लिये production, नहीं एक्टिंग ), और an ऑस्कर.
in addition, गोल्डबर्ग रै a अंग्रेजों अकादमी फिल्मी Award, four लोगों 's Choice पुरस्कार, and has महरूम सम्मानित साथ a star on the हॉलीवुड चलना of कीर्ति.
She is one of the few मनोरंजनकर्ता जो have जीती an एमी, Grammy, ऑस्कर, और टोनी Award.
Augusta is a संचित नगर in the u.S. राज्य of Georgia, स्तिथ at the पतन line of the savannah नदी, at the head of इसके navigable portion.
As of the 2010 census, the Augusta– रिचमंड काउंटी population थी 195,844 नहीं गिनती the unconsolidated शहरों of hephzibah और blythe.
augusta is the principal नगर of the augusta – Richmond काउंटी Metropolitan सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रफल, which as of 2010 had an अनुमानित जनसांख्यिकी of 556,877, making it both the second-largest नगर और the second-largest मैट्रो area in the राज्य after अटलांटा.
It is the 116th-largest city in the संयुक्त States.
Internationally, Augusta is बेहतरीन ज्ञात लिये होस्टिंग The Masters टूर्नामेंट in golf प्रत्येक वसन्त.
A CD-ROM ( ) is a pre-pressed कॉम्पैक्ट disc which contains आंकड़ा.
the name is an एक्रोनिम which स्टैंड लिये `` कॉम्पैक्ट डिस्क Read-only मेमोरी ``.
कंप्यूटर can पढ़ा cd-roms, but can not write on उन्हें.
cd-roms हैं popularly प्रयुक्त to distribute computer software, सहित वीडियो games और मल्टीमीडिया applications, हालांकि any आंकड़ा can be भंडारित ( up to the क्षमता सीमा of a disc ).
कुछ CDs, called उन्नत cds, थाम दोनो computer data और ऑडियो with the latter सक्षम of being played on a cd player, while आंकड़ा ( ऐसे as तन्त्र or digital video ) is only usable on a computer ( ऐसे as आईएसओ 9660 format pc cd-roms ).
The पीला Book is the technical standard कि defines the स्वरूप of cd-roms.
One of a set of color-bound किताबे कि contain the तकनीकी विशेषताएँ लिये all CD स्वरुप, the Yellow किताब, निर्मित by सोनी and Philips, was the first एक्सटेंशन of Compact डिस्क डिजिटल ऑडियो.
It adapted the format to थाम कोई रूप of data.
the Chicago ब्लैकहॉक्स ( spelled as ब्लैक चीलों before 1986, and known colloquially as the Hawks ) हैं a पेशेवर बर्फ हॉकी team based in Chicago, Illinois.
वे are सदस्यों of the सेंट्रल प्रभाग of the Western Conference of the National Hockey लीग ( NHL ).
वे have जीती four स्टेनली Cup championships चूंकि their founding in 1926, most recently in 2009–10.
the ब्लैकहॉक्स are एक of the असली छह NHL टीमों, along साथ the Detroit Red विंग्स, मॉन्ट्रियल canadiens, Toronto Maple leafs, Boston bruins और नई यॉर्क रेंजरों.
चूंकि the Blackhawks have played their घर खेल at the संयुक्त बीच after having spent 65 सालो playing at Chicago Stadium.

the बैंगनी color is प्रायः संबद्ध साथ penance and detachment.
समान Christian penitential practice is seen in अन्य Catholic countries, sometimes संबद्ध with mortification of the flesh.
granada, निकारागुआ.
lent ( लैटिन : Quadragesima ) is a solemn observance in the liturgical साल of many Christian denominations, स्थायी for a काल of approximately छह weeks अग्रणी up to ईस्टर Sunday.
in the general Latin-rite और सबसे पश्चिमी denominations Lent is taken to run इससे राख बुधवार to Maundy गुरुवार ( पावन गुरुवार ) morning or to ईस्टर Eve.
in the Catholic Church, lent lasts जबतक Holy गुरुवार, while अन्य denominations run until ईस्टर संध्या.
The परंपरागत purpose of lent is the preparation of the believer through prayer, penance, तौबा, almsgiving, और self-denial.
इसके संस्थागत purpose is heightened in the annual commemoration of पावन सप्ताह, marking the death, burial और क़यामत of यीशु, which recalls the events of the Bible when Jesus is crucified on शुभ शुक्रवार, जिससे तब culminates in the celebration on ईस्टर Sunday of the Resurrection of Jesus मसीह.
During lent, अनेक of the वफादार कमिट to उपवास or giving up certain प्रकार of luxuries as a रूप of penitence.
the स्टेशन of the क्रॉस, a devotional commemoration of मसीह 's carrying the क्रॉस और of उसके निष्पादन, हैं प्रायः observed.
Many रोमन Catholic and कुछ प्रोटोस्टेंट churches हटाएँ flowers from उनके altars, जबकि crucifixes, धार्मिक मूर्तियाँ, and other elaborate religious symbols are प्रायः रहमत in बैंगनी fabrics in solemn observance of the इवेंट.
in certain pious कैथोलिक countries, some adherents mark the ऋतु साथ the traditional abstention इससे the consumption of meat.
in some countries, ग्रैंड धार्मिक processions and सांस्कृतिक कस्टम हैं observed, और the वफादार attempt to visit सात चर्च during पावन सप्ताह in सम्मान of यीशु Christ heading to Mount कलवारी.
lent is traditionally described as स्थायी for forty दिनों, in commemoration of the चालीस days which, according to the gospels of Matthew, चिह्नित and ल्यूक, Jesus खर्च fasting in the मरुस्थल पहले the beginning of उसके public मंत्रालय, where he endured temptation by the Devil.
However, different ईसाई denominations गणना the forty दिनों of Lent differently.
In most Western traditions the Sundays are नहीं counted as भाग of Lent ; यूँ the काल इससे राख Wednesday जबतक ईस्टर consists of 40 दिनों जब the Sundays हैं excluded.
However in the Roman Catholic गिरिजाघर lent is अभी लिया to समाप्त on Holy Thursday बल्कि than ईस्टर संध्या, और hence lasts 38 दिनों excluding sundays, or 44 दिनों in कुल.
इस इवेंट, along साथ इसके परहेज़गारों कस्टम हैं observed by catholics, lutherans, methodists, Presbyterians, and Anglicans.
स्थान of Chernobyl nuclear शक्ति संयंत्र
The abandoned नगर of Pripyat साथ chernobyl संयंत्र in the अलहदा
abandoned housing ब्लॉक in pripyat
The chernobyl विपत्ति (, Chornobylska Katastrofa – chornobyl Catastrophe ) थी a catastrophic नाभिकीय दुर्घटना कि occurred on 26 अप्रैल 1986 at the chernobyl नाभिकीय शक्ति Plant in Ukraine ( तब officially the Ukrainian SSR ), which थी अंतर्गत the direct क्षेत्राधिकार of the central authorities of the सोवियत Union.
an विस्फोट और आग released large quantities of radioactive अणु into the माहौल, जिससे स्प्रेड over much of the पश्चिमी ussr and Europe.
the Chernobyl disaster is widely considered to have महरूम the worst नाभिकीय power संयंत्र accident in इतिहास, and is एक of तभी two classified as a स्तर 7 इवेंट on the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Nuclear इवेंट Scale ( the अन्य होने the Fukushima daiichi नाभिकीय disaster in 2011 ).
the बैटल to contain the संदूषण and avert a वृहद प्रलय ultimately involved over 500,000 मजदूर and cost an अनुमानित 18 billion rubles.
the official सोवियत casualty count of 31 deaths रै been विवादित, and long-term effects such as cancers and deformities हैं स्टिल होने accounted लिये.
in व्याकरण, a subject पूरक is a predicative अभिव्यक्ति that फ़ॉलो a linking verb ( copula ) और that complements ( completes ) the विषय of the sentence by either ( 1 ) renaming it or ( 2 ) describing it.
In the former मामला, a renaming noun phrase ऐसे as a noun or pronoun is पुकारा a predicative nominal.
an adjective following the copula and describing the subject is पुकारा a predicative क्रियाशील.
In either case the predicative पूरक in effect mirrors the विषय.
Subject complements are प्रयुक्त साथ a छोटी क्लास of क्रियाएँ called linking verbs or copula, of which be is the सबसे आम.
Since copula हैं stative क्रियाएँ, विषय complements are नहीं प्रभावित by any कार्रवाई of the क्रिया.
Subject complements are typically नहीं clause arguments, nor are वे clause केंद्रीभूत.
throughout the fifty-five साल history of the ग्रैमी पुरस्कार, many significant रिकॉर्ड have been set.
इस पेज only शामिल the प्रतिस्पर्धी पुरस्कार won by various कलाकारों.
This does नहीं include the विभिन्न special पुरस्कार कि are presented by the National Academy of रिकॉर्डिंग कला और sciences such as Lifetime उपलब्धि Awards, trustees पुरस्कार, Technical पुरस्कार or Legend पुरस्कार.
the page however करता include अन्य non-performance सम्बन्धित Grammys ( known as the Craft & Production Fields ) कि may have महरूम प्रस्तुत to the artist ( s ).
Marshall Bruce mathers iii ( born October 17, 1972 ), बेहतर ज्ञात by उसके stage नाम Eminem ( stylized as eminǝm ) and by his alter ego Slim छायादार, is an अमरीकी rapper, रिकार्ड निर्माता, songwriter और कर्ता.
Eminem, along साथ his सोलो career, is a सदस्य of उसके समूह d12, और also one हाफ of the hip हॉप duo Bad meets दुष्ट, साथ Royce da 5'9 ''.
Eminem is one of the best-selling कलाकारों in the संसार और is the best-selling कलाकार of the 2000s.
He has been सूचीबद्ध और क्रमित as एक of the greatest कलाकारों of सब समय by many magazines, including Rolling Stone magazine which ranked him 82nd on its सूची of the 100 महानतम Artists of सब समय.
The वही पत्रिका घोषित him the किंग of Hip Hop.
Including his कार्य with D12 and ख़राब Meets दुष्ट, एमिनेम has हासिल ten number-one albums on the Billboard 200.
he has sold अधिक than 100 लाख records worldwide, सहित 42 लाख tracks and 49.1 लाख एल्बम in the संयुक्त राज्य.
as an भूमिगत rapper Eminem released his डेब्यू solo album, अनन्त in 1996.
The एल्बम was a नाजुक और वाणिज्यिक failure.
he gained mainstream popularity in 1999 बाद the release of his major-label डेब्यू एल्बम the पतला Shady lp.
The LP भी earned Eminem उसके पहला Grammy Award लिये बेहतरीन रैप Album.
उसके next दो records the मार्शल mathers LP, and the Eminem दिखाएँ, भी जीती बेहतरीन रैप Album ग्रैमी पुरस्कार, making एमिनेम the पहला artist to जीत बेहतरीन रैप Album for तीन consecutive एलपी.
This थी followed by another studio रिलीज in 2004 titled encore.
एमिनेम तब गई on अंतराल after touring in 2005.

Eminem जीती Grammy पुरस्कार for दोनो Relapse and रिकवरी, giving him a total of 13 grammys in his career.
Eminem रै खोली अन्य ventures, सहित his own रिकार्ड लेबल Shady रिकॉर्ड साथ his मैनेजर पॉल Rosenberg.
he also has उसके अपना रेडियो channel, शेड 45 on sirius XM रेडियो.

He has also made कैमियो दिखावे in The Wash ( 2001 ), मजेदार लोगों ( 2009 ) and the television श्रेणी अनुगामी.
the एकड़ is a ईकाई of क्षेत्रफल प्रयुक्त in the इम्पीरियल and U.S. प्रथागत प्रणालियों.
an एकड़ is about 40 % of a hectare – थोड़ा छोटी than an American football field.
The एकड़ is no longer commonly used, हालांकि a few notable अपवाद include the United States, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, Burma और the संयुक्त Kingdom ( as of 2010, the एकड़ is no longer officially used in the United किंगडम, though is still प्रयुक्त in real एस्टेट descriptions ).
it is स्टिल used, to some extent, in Canada.
The अंतरराष्ट्रीय प्रतीक of the एकड़ is ac, और is पारिभाषित as 1/640 of a वर्गाकार mile.
the सबसे commonly प्रयुक्त एकड़ today is the अंतरराष्ट्रीय एकड़.
in the संयुक्त राज्य दोनो the अंतरराष्ट्रीय acre और the slightly अलग us सर्वेक्षण acre are in use.
The सबसे common उपयोग of the एकड़ is to measure tracts of land.
One अंतरराष्ट्रीय acre is पारिभाषित as 4046.8564224 square मीटर.
दौरान the Middle Ages, an एकड़ थी the राशि of जमीन कि could be plowed in एक दिन साथ a yoke of oxen.
एंटोनी लाव्वाज़्ये 's डिस्कवरी of the विधि of संरक्षण of द्रव्यमान led to अनेक new findings in the 19th सदी.
जोसेफ proust 's विधि of definite proportions और जॉन डाल्टन 's परमाणु सिद्धान्त branched इससे the discoveries of एंटोनी Lavoisier.
Lavoisier 's quantitative प्रयोग revealed that दहन involved oxygen rather than कया was previously thought to be phlogiston.
the विधि of conservation of द्रव्यमान, or principle of mass conservation, states that लिये कोई प्रणाली closed to all transfers of पदार्थ और उर्जा ( दोनो of which have द्रव्यमान ), the द्रव्यमान of the system must remain constant over समय, as system द्रव्यमान can not change मात्रा if it is not added or removed.
Hence, the मात्रा of mass is `` conserved '' over समय.
the विधि implies कि mass can neither be निर्मित nor नष्ट, although it may be rearranged in स्पेस, or the entities associated with it may be बदला in form, as for उदाहरण when लाइट or शारीरिक work is transformed into अणु कि contribute the वही द्रव्यमान to the प्रणाली as the लाइट or कार्य had contributed.
the law implies ( requires ) कि दौरान any chemical reaction, नाभिकीय प्रतिक्रिया, or रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय in an पृथक प्रणाली, the mass of the reactants or starting सामग्री जरूर equal the mass of the उत्पाद.
The अवधारणा of द्रव्यमान संरक्षण is widely used in many फ़ील्ड ऐसे as रसायन, यांत्रिकी, and द्रव dynamics.
historically, द्रव्यमान conservation was खोजा in chemical प्रतिक्रियाएँ by एंटोनी Lavoisier in the late 18th सदी, और थी of crucial महत्व in the प्रगति from alchemy to the आधुनिक प्राकृतिक science of रसायन.
The closely सम्बन्धित अवधारणा of matter संरक्षण was मिला to थाम good in रसायन to ऐसे ऊँची approximation कि it failed only लिये the high energies treated by the later refinements of आपेक्षिकता सिद्धान्त, but otherwise remains useful और fear सटीक for most chemical calculations, even in modern practice.
in खास आपेक्षिकता, needed for accuracy when large energy हस्तांतरण between systems is involved, the अंतर between thermodynamically closed और isolated systems becomes important, since संरक्षण of mass is सख्ती और perfectly upheld तभी लिये so-called isolated प्रणालियों, i.e. those completely isolated इससे सब exchanges साथ the पर्यावरण.
in this परिस्थिति, the mass-energy equivalence theorem states कि द्रव्यमान conservation is equivalent to total energy conservation, which is the पहला विधि of ऊष्मागतिकी.
by contrast, लिये a thermodynamically बंद प्रणाली ( i.e., एक जिससे is बंद to exchanges of matter, but खोलें to exchanges of non-material उर्जा, ऐसे as ऊष्मा और कार्य, with the परिवेश ) mass is ( usually ) तभी लगभग conserved.
the इनपुट or output of non-material energy जरूर change the द्रव्यमान of the प्रणाली in आपेक्षिकता theory, हालांकि the change is प्रायः small, since अपेक्षाकृत विशाल amounts of such energy ( by comparison with ordinary अनुभव ) carry तभी a छोटी राशि of mass ( again by ordinary मानकों of मापन ).
In खास relativity, द्रव्यमान is not परिवर्तित to उर्जा, चूंकि energy in सब of its फ़ॉर्म सदा retains its equivalent राशि of द्रव्यमान throughout कोई परिवर्तन or translocation into, or आउट of, a system.
however, निश्चित प्रकार of पदार्थ ( a अलग concept ) may be परिवर्तित to उर्जा, so long as the mass of the system is unchanged in the process.
however, if ऐसे energy is removed from systems, they must lose the द्रव्यमान that is associated with it.
In सामान्य relativity, द्रव्यमान ( और energy ) conservation in expanding volumes of स्पेस is a जटिल अवधारणा, subject to अलग definitions, और neither द्रव्यमान nor energy is as सख्ती और बस conserved as is the मामला in special आपेक्षिकता and in मिन्कोवस्की स्पेस.
For a discussion, देखिए द्रव्यमान in सामान्य relativity.
a सुअर is कोई of the पशु in the genus सस, within the suidae family of even-toed ungulates.
सूअर include the domestic pig, इसके पूर्वज the जंगली boar, and अनेक अन्य wild relatives.

A 3.5-inch diskette 's `` floppy '' चुम्बकीय सामग्री, removed from इसके आवास
A floppy disk, or diskette, is a डिस्क भंडार medium composed of a डिस्क of thin और flexible चुम्बकीय storage मीडियम, sealed in a आयताकार plastic carrier lined साथ कपड़ा that removes धूल अणु.
वे हैं read और लिखा by a फ्लॉपी डिस्क ड्राइव ( FDD ).
फ्लॉपी डिस्क, initially as मीडिया और later in and 3.5-inch ( 90 mm ) आकार, यहूद a ubiquitous रूप of आंकड़ा storage and एक्सचेंज इससे the mid-1970s well into the पहला decade of the 21st century.
by 2010, कंप्यूटर motherboards यहूद rarely manufactured with फ्लॉपी ड्राइव support ; `` floppies could be used as an external usb ड्राइव, but ``, 8 ``, और non-standard ड्राइव could तभी be handled by बूढ़ा उपकरण.
जबकि फ्लॉपी disk ड्राइव still have some सीमित उपयोग, especially with legacy औद्योगिक computer equipment, वे have been superseded by आंकड़ा भंडार विधि साथ much वृहद capacity, ऐसे as usb फ्लैश drives, portable external hard डिस्क drives, optical discs, memory ताश, और कंप्यूटर संजाल.

in बेसबॉल, a कटर, or काटें fastball, is a प्रकार of fastball जिससे breaks slightly toward the पिचर 's दस्ताने पक्ष as it पहुँच home plate.
This पिच is कही between a स्लाइडर and a fastball, as it is प्रायः thrown faster than a स्लाइडर but साथ more motion than a ठेठ fastball.
कुछ pitchers उपयोग a कटर as a रास्ता to prevent hitters from expecting their नियमित fastballs.
a common तकनीक प्रयुक्त to throw a कटर is to उपयोग a four-seam fastball पकड़ साथ the बेसबॉल set slightly बंद center in the hand.
When a batter is समर्थ to hit a कटर पिच, it often results in soft सम्पर्क and an easy out, due to the पिच 's गति keeping the बॉल away इससे the चमगादड़ 's मीठी स्पॉट.
the cutter is typically 2–5 किमी slower than a पिचर 's four-seam fastball.
in 2010, the औसत पिच classified as a cutter by pitchf/x thrown by a right-handed pitcher थी 88.6 किमी ; the औसत four-seamer थी 92.1 mph.

Odysseus ( or ; यूनानी :, ), भी ज्ञात by the Roman नाम ulysses ( ; ), was a legendary यूनानी king of ithaca और a hero of होमर 's एपिक poem the Odyssey.
Odysseus भी plays a key role in होमर 's इलियड and अन्य works in कि same एपिक साईकिल.
husband of पेनेलोप, पिता of telemachus, और बेटे of Laërtes ( or sisyphus ) and Anticlea, odysseus is प्रसिद्ध लिये उसके brilliance, छल, और versatility ( polytropos ), और is hence ज्ञात by the epithet Odysseus the Cunning ( mētis, or `` cunning प्रज्ञा `` ).
he is सबसे प्रसिद्ध लिये the टेन eventful सालो he took to return home बाद the decade-long Trojan युद्ध और his प्रसिद्ध Trojan घोड़ा ploy to कैप्चर the city of Troy.
erie is a Statutory कस्बा in बोल्डर और Weld counties in the U.S. state of Colorado.
the जनसांख्यिकी according to the 2010 जनसांख्यिकी is 18,135 और was अंकित as 6,291 at the 2000 census.
the कस्बा of Erie is located बस west of i-25 लिये आसान access to I-70, डेनवर अंतरराष्ट्रीय विमानक्षेत्र and कोलोराडो 's entire Front Range.
erie 's नियोजन Area spans 48 वर्गाकार miles, extending इससे the उत्तर पक्ष of State Highway 52 दक्षिण to State राजमार्ग 7, and between US 287 on the west and अंतरराज्यीय 25 to the east.
erie is approximately 35 minutes इससे Denver अंतरराष्ट्रीय विमानक्षेत्र, 25 minutes to डेनवर और 20 minutes इससे बोल्डर.
The फलक of trustees serves as the विधान और governing देह of the Town of erie और is जिम्मेदार for establishing कस्बा policies and लक्ष्य.
The Board रै the प्राधिकार to अपनाना कानून, ordinances और रिज़ॉल्यूशन as needed to conduct the business of the कस्बा, और by अध्यादेश may डालें into contracts or intergovernmental समझौतों to furnish, प्राप्त सेवाएं or to provide for cooperative सेवा डिलीवरी.
Appointed by and सेवारत at the pleasure of the फलक of trustees, the कस्बा व्यवस्थापक is the chief ऑपरेटिंग और प्रशासनिक अधिकारी of the कस्बा and is जिम्मेदार लिये providing पेशेवर नेतृत्व in the administration and निष्पादन of policies और उद्देश्य प्रतिपादित by the Board.
the mission of the erie पुलिस विभाग is to communicate and कार्य साथ the जातियाँ to maintain a safe पर्यावरण, prevent अपराधों और enforce the विधि, while protecting the अधिकारों of सब.

The प्रमुख runway is concrete प्रशस्त and 4,700 फीट long.

साल्वाडोर Domingo Felipe Jacinto dalí i domènech, 1st Marqués de dalí de Pubol ( May 11, 1904january 23, 1989 ), known as Salvador dalí ( ), was a prominent स्पेनी surrealist painter born in figueres, स्पेन.
Dalí थी a skilled draftsman, बेहतरीन ज्ञात for the striking and विचित्र images in उसके surrealist कार्य.
उसके painterly skills हैं often attributed to the influence of Renaissance मास्टर्स.
उसके best-known work, the हठ of मेमोरी, थी समाप्त in 1931.
dalí 's expansive कलाकारी रंगमंडल included film, मूर्तिकला, and photography, in सहयोग साथ a range of कलाकारों in a किस्में of मीडिया.
dalí attributed his `` love of everything that is gilded और excessive, my जुनून for लक्ज़री और my love of प्राच्य clothes '' to a self-styled `` अरब lineage '', claiming कि उसके ancestors were descended इससे the Moors.
dalí थी highly imaginative, और भी enjoyed indulging in असामान्य और वैभवशाली बर्ताव.
उसके eccentric manner और attention-grabbing public क्रियाएँ sometimes drew अधिक ध्यान than his कलाकृति, to the dismay of those जो आयोजित his कार्य in high esteem, और to the irritation of उसके आलोचकों.

The मानवता हैं academic disciplines that पढ़ाई इंसान culture, using विधि कि हैं primarily विश्लेषणात्मक, critical, or speculative, and having a significant ऐतिहासिक तत्व, as distinguished इससे the mainly अनुभवजन्य approaches of the natural sciences.
the मानवता include ancient and आधुनिक languages, साहित्य, philosophy, धर्म, और विज़ुअल and performing arts ऐसे as music and थिएटर.
the humanities that हैं also regarded as सोशल sciences include history, anthropology, क्षेत्रफल studies, संचार अध्ययन, सांस्कृतिक studies, विधि, economics और linguistics.
विद्वानों working in the मानवता हैं sometimes वर्णित as `` humanists ''.
however, कि पद भी describes the philosophical position of मानवतावाद, जिससे some `` antihumanist `` विद्वानों in the humanities अस्वीकृत.
Some द्वितीयक schools offer मानवता classes, usually consisting of अंग्रेज़ी literature, वैश्विक studies, और art.
इंसान disciplines जैसे इतिहास, सांस्कृतिक anthropology and मनोविश्लेषण पढ़ाई विषय matters to which the प्रायोगिक विधि करता नहीं apply, and वे have अभिगम instead to the तुलनात्मक method और तुलनात्मक research.

The White हाउस क्रिसमस Tree, also ज्ञात as the ब्लू Room Christmas Tree, is the आधिकारिक indoor क्रिसमस पेड़ at the निवास of the President of the संयुक्त States, the White हाउस.
The पहला अंदर क्रिसमस tree थी संस्थापित in the White House sometime in the 19th century ( there हैं varying claims as to the exact साल ) and चूंकि 1961 the tree has had a प्रसंग मोटिफ at the discretion of the पहला Lady of the United राज्य.
the President of the संयुक्त राज्य of अमेरिका ( potus ) is the सिर of राज्य and सिर of सरकारी of the संयुक्त राज्य.
The president लीड the कार्यपालिका शाखा of the संघीय सरकारी and is the commander-in-chief of the United राज्य हथियारबंद शक्तियां.
Article ii of the U.S. संविधान vests the executive शक्ति of the संयुक्त राज्य in the अध्यक्ष और आरोप उसे साथ the निष्पादन of federal law, alongside the responsibility of appointing federal executive, राजनयिक, regulatory, and न्यायिक अधिकारियों, and concluding treaties साथ विदेशी शक्तियां, साथ the सलाह and consent of the Senate.
The president is further empowered to grant संघीय pardons और reprieves, और to convene और adjourn either or both घरों of कॉंग्रेस under extraordinary circumstances.
Since the founding of the United राज्य, the शक्ति of the अध्यक्ष और the संघीय सरकारी have grown substantially और each आधुनिक president, despite possessing no औपचारिक legislative शक्तियां परे signing or vetoing congressionally passed बिल्स, is largely जिम्मेदार for dictating the विधान agenda of उसके पार्टी और the विदेशी and घरेलू नीति of the संयुक्त राज्य.
the अध्यक्ष is अक्सर described as the सबसे powerful person in the संसार.
The अध्यक्ष is indirectly निर्वाचित by the लोगों through the चुनावी College to a four-year पद, और is one of only two nationally elected संघीय officers, the अन्य being the वाइस अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States.
The Twenty-second Amendment, adopted in 1951, prohibits anyone from कभी होने निर्वाचित to the प्रेसिडेंसी लिये a तीसरा पूरा पद.
it भी prohibits a व्यक्ति इससे होने elected to the प्रेसिडेंसी अधिक than एकबार if कि person previously था परोसा as president, or acting president, for अधिक than दो years of another व्यक्ति 's पद as अध्यक्ष.
In सब, 43 individuals have served 55 four-year शर्तें.
On जनवरी 20, 2009, बराक ओबामा became the 44th and current अध्यक्ष.
On नवम्बर 6, 2012, he was re-elected और is अनुसूचित to serve जबतक January 20, 2017.
Senses हैं physiological capacities of organisms that provide आंकड़ा for बोध.
The होश और उनके आपरेशन, classification, and theory are अतिव्यापी विषय studied by a किस्में of फ़ील्ड, सबसे notably neuroscience, संज्ञानात्मक मनोविज्ञान ( or संज्ञानात्मक विज्ञान ), और दर्शनशास्त्र of perception.
the nervous प्रणाली has a विशिष्ट sensory प्रणाली or अंग, dedicated to each sense.
Humans have a multitude of होश.
Sight ( ophthalmoception ), सुनना ( audioception ), स्वाद ( gustaoception ), smell ( olfacoception or olfacception ), और touch ( tactioception ) are the पाँच traditionally पहचाना.
While the ability to detect other stimuli परे those governed by the परंपरागत होश exists, सहित temperature ( thermoception ), kinesthetic भाव ( proprioception ), pain ( nociception ), balance ( equilibrioception ), acceleration ( kinesthesioception ), और विभिन्न internal stimuli ( e.g. the अलग chemoreceptors for detecting नमक and कार्बन डाइऑक्साइड concentrations in the blood ), only a छोटी क्रमांक of these can safely be वर्गीकृत as पृथक senses in and of themselves.
What constitutes a भाव is a पदार्थ of कुछ बहस, leading to difficulties in defining कया exactly a sense is.
Animals also have receptors to sense the संसार around them, with डिग्री of capability varying greatly between प्रजाति.
इंसानो have a comparatively कमजोर sense of smell, while कुछ पशु may lack one or अधिक of the traditional पाँच senses.
Some पशु may also सेवन और interpret संवेदी stimuli in बहुत अलग ways.
Some species of पशु हैं able to sense the संसार in a रास्ता कि humans can नहीं, साथ कुछ प्रजाति able to भाव विद्युत और चुम्बकीय fields, और detect water pressure और currents.
मकड़ियों ( order Araneae ) are air-breathing arthropods कि have आठ टाँगे और chelicerae with fangs that इंजेक्ट venom.
वे हैं the largest order of arachnids और रैंक सातवाँ in कुल species diversity among सब other groups of जीवों.
मकड़ियों हैं found worldwide on every महाद्वीप मगर for अंटार्कटिक, and have become स्थापित in nearly every आवास with the exception of air और sea colonization.
as of 2008, at least 43,678 spider प्रजाति, और 109 परिवारों have महरूम अंकित by taxonomists ; however, वहीँ has been confusion भीतर the scientific जातियाँ as to कैसा सब ये families चाहिए be classified, as evidenced by the over 20 different classifications कि have महरूम प्रस्तावित चूंकि 1900.
anatomically, मकड़ियों differ इससे अन्य arthropods in कि the usual देह खण्ड हैं fused into two tagmata, the cephalothorax और उदर, and joined by a small, बेलनाकार pedicel.
नापसंद कीट, मकड़ियों do नहीं have antennae.
in सब except the सबसे primitive समूह, the Mesothelae, मकड़ियों have the सबसे centralized बेचैन systems of all arthropods, as सब उनके ganglia are fused into one द्रव्यमान in the cephalothorax.
Unlike most arthropods, मकड़ियों have no extensor muscles in उनके limbs and instead extend उन्हें by हाइड्रोलिक pressure.
उनके abdomens भालू appendages कि have महरूम modified into spinnerets कि extrude रेशा from up to छह प्रकार of रेशा ग्रंथियों within उनके उदर.
मकड़ी webs vary widely in आकार, shape और the राशि of स्टिकी लड़ी used.
it now appears that the सर्पिल orb web may be एक of the earliest forms, और spiders कि produce उलझे cobwebs are अधिक abundant और diverse than orb-web मकड़ियों.
Spider-like arachnids साथ silk-producing spigots appeared in the devonian काल about, but these animals जाहिर lacked spinnerets.
True मकड़ियों have महरूम found in carboniferous रॉक्स from, और हैं बहुत similar to the सबसे primitive surviving order, the mesothelae.
the प्रमुख समूह of आधुनिक spiders, Mygalomorphae and araneomorphae, पहला appeared in the triassic काल, before.
A herbivorous species, bagheera kiplingi, थी described in 2008, but सब अन्य ज्ञात प्रजाति are परभक्षी, ज़्यादातर preying on insects और on अन्य मकड़ियों, although a few large प्रजाति भी take पक्षियों और lizards.
मकड़ियों उपयोग a चौड़ी range of रणनीति to capture शिकार : trapping it in स्टिकी webs, lassoing it साथ स्टिकी bolas, mimicking the prey to avoid detection, or कार्यशील it bas.
सबसे detect शिकार mainly by संवेदन vibrations, लकिन the क्रियाशील hunters have acute vision, and hunters of the genus portia show signs of प्रज्ञा in उनके choice of tactics and ability to develop नई ones.
मकड़ियों ' गुस्ताखी are too narrow to लो solids, और वे liquidize उनके food by बाढ़ it साथ digestive एंजाइमों और grinding it साथ the bases of उनके pedipalps, as वे do not have true जबड़े.
Male मकड़ियों पहचानो themselves by a variety of जटिल courtship संस्कार to avoid होने eaten by the महिलाओं.
males of सबसे species जीवित a few matings, limited mainly by their छोटी जीवन spans.
Females बुनते रेशा egg-cases, each of which may contain hundreds of अंडे.
महिलाओं of अनेक प्रजाति परवाह लिये their young, for उदाहरण by carrying them around or by sharing खाना साथ उन्हें.
a minority of प्रजाति are सोशल, भवन communal webs that may house anywhere from a few to 50,000 individuals.
सोशल behavior सीमाएँ इससे precarious toleration, as in the विधवा spiders, to co-operative शिकार और food-sharing.
हालांकि सबसे spiders live for at सबसे two सालो, tarantulas and other mygalomorph spiders can सजीव up to 25 years in captivity.
जबकि the venom of a few प्रजाति is खतरनाक to humans, scientists हैं अभी researching the उपयोग of spider venom in medicine and as non-polluting pesticides.
Spider silk provides a संयोजन of lightness, शक्ति and elasticity कि is श्रेष्ठ to कि of सिंथेटिक सामग्री, और मकड़ी रेशा जीनों have been inserted into स्तनधारियों और पौधे to देखिए if these can be प्रयुक्त as silk कारखानों.
As a result of उनके चौड़ी range of behaviors, मकड़ियों have become आम प्रतीकों in art और mythology symbolizing various combinations of patience, क्रूरता और रचनात्मक शक्तियां.
धूसर 's Anatomy is an American टेलीविज़न medical drama that premiered on the American प्रसारण कम्पनी ( एबीसी ), as a mid-season बदलना on March 27, 2005.
The श्रेणी रै aired नौ सीज़न, और focuses on the fictional जीवनदान of सर्जिकल interns and निवासियों as वे gradually evolve into seasoned doctors, while trying to maintain निजी lives.
the show 's premise originated with Shonda Rhimes, जो serves as an executive निर्माता, along with बेट्सी Beers, चिह्नित गॉर्डन, क्रिस्टा Vernoff, रोब Corn, चिह्नित Wilding, और Allan Heinberg.
the series was created to be racially विविध, utilizing a color-blind casting तकनीक.
It is primarily फिल्माया in लॉस Angeles, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
the श्रेणी ' समर्थक is dr. मेरेडिथ धूसर ( Ellen pompeo ), जो originally is accepted into the residency program at the fictional Seattle अनुग्रह हॉस्पिटल.
Meredith is आबंटित to work under dr. Miranda Bailey ( चन्द्रा विल्सन ), साथ with Dr. Cristina Yang ( Sandra oh ), dr. George O'Malley ( T. R. नाईट ), dr. Izzie Stevens ( कैथरीन Heigl ), और dr. Alex Karev ( जस्टिन Chambers ).
following O'Malley 's मौत और Stevens ' departure, the हॉस्पिटल 's विलय with रहमत West brings in Dr. जैक्सन एवेरी ( जेसी Williams ) and Dr. अप्रैल kepner ( सारा खींचा ), in the sixth ऋतु.

Dr. Preston Burke ( यशायाह वॉशिंगटन ) departs at the निष्कर्ष of the तीसरा ऋतु, and is replaced by Dr. एरिका hahn ( ब्रुक Smith ), who पत्ते the दिखाएँ during the fifth season, and later dr. टेडी Altman ( Kim Raver ), who departs at the समाप्त of the eighth ऋतु.

dr. callie Torres ( Sara रामिरेज़ ) और Dr. Mark स्लोअन ( eric Dane ) also डालें the दिखाएँ in the second ऋतु, while the latter मरता in the प्रीमियर of the ninth ऋतु.
Meredith 's half-sister, Dr. Lexie धूसर ( chyler Leigh ), appears from season तीन और dies at the समाप्त of season आठ.

धूसर 's Anatomy is the highest-rated नाटक in the कुंजी 18–49 demographic.
Previously among the overall top-ten रेटेड shows in the संयुक्त राज्य, Grey 's anatomy रै महरूम खूब प्राप्त by आलोचकों.
Considered an प्रभाव on संस्कृति, the series has received numerous पुरस्कार, और has भी महरूम शामिल in विभिन्न आलोचकों ' top ten सूचियाँ.

schizophrenia ( or ) is a दिमागी विकार characterized by a विश्लेषण of thought processes और by a deficit of ठेठ emotional responses.
आम लक्षण शामिल auditory मति, paranoid or bizarre delusions, or disorganized वाक and thinking, और it is accompanied by significant सोशल or occupational dysfunction.
the onset of symptoms typically occurs in यंग adulthood, with a वैश्विक आजीवन व्यापकता of परिचय 0.3–0.7 %.
निदान is आधारित on observed बर्ताव और the रोगी 's reported अनुभवों.
आनुवंशिकी, जल्दी पर्यावरण, neurobiology, and मनोवैज्ञानिक और सोशल प्रक्रियाओं appear to be महत्वपूर्ण contributory factors ; कुछ recreational and नुस्खा drugs appear to cause or worsen लक्षण.
Current शोध is केन्द्रित on the भूमिका of neurobiology, हालांकि no सिंगल पृथक organic cause has महरूम मिला.
The अनेक possible combinations of symptoms have triggered debate about whether the निदान represents a single विकार or a क्रमांक of अलहदा syndromes.
Despite the etymology of the पद from the यूनानी जड़ें skhizein ( σχίζειν, `` to split '' ) और phrēn, phren- ( φρήν, φρεν- ; `` दिमाग '' ), schizophrenia करता not imply a `` split personality '', or `` अनेक व्यक्तित्व विकार '' ( which is ज्ञात these days as dissociative पहचान विकार ) —a condition with जिससे it is often उलझन in पब्लिक बोध.
बल्कि, the term अर्थात् a `` splitting of दिमागी functions '', क्युकी of the symptomatic प्रस्तुतीकरण of the illness.
the mainstay of treatment is antipsychotic medication, जिससे primarily suppresses dopamine ( and sometimes serotonin ) receptor कार्यकलाप.
Psychotherapy और वोकेशनल और सोशल rehabilitation हैं भी महत्वपूर्ण in उपचार.
in अधिक गंभीर cases—where वहीँ is risk to स्वः and others— involuntary hospitalization may be जरुरी, हालांकि हॉस्पिटल stays हैं अभी shorter और less बारंबार than वे एकबार यहूद.
the disorder is विचार मुख्यतः to affect cognition, लकिन it also usually contributes to दीर्घकालिक समस्याएं with behavior और जज्बात.
लोगों with schizophrenia are likely to have additional ( comorbid ) शर्तें, सहित major अवसाद और anxiety विकार ; the आजीवन occurrence of substance उपयोग disorder is लगभग 50 %.
सोशल problems, ऐसे as long-term बेरोजगारी, गरीबी, और homelessness are common.
The औसत जीवन प्रत्याशा of people साथ the विकार is 12 to 15 सालो कम than those बगैर, the result of increased शारीरिक health समस्याएं और a उच्चतर suicide रेट ( परिचय 5 % ).

the एपिक of Gilgamesh, an एपिक कविता from मेसोपोटामिया, is amongst the earliest surviving works of साहित्य.
The साहित्यिक इतिहास of gilgamesh begins साथ five स्वतंत्र Sumerian poems परिचय 'bilgamesh ' ( sumerian लिये Gilgamesh ), king of uruk.
चार of ये यहूद प्रयुक्त as सोर्स material लिये a combined epic in Akkadian.
इस पहला combined एपिक, ज्ञात as the `` Old babylonian '' संस्करण, dates to the 18th सदी bc and is titled बाद its incipit, Shūtur एली sharrī ( `` surpassing सब अन्य किंग्स '' ).
तभी a few fragments of it have बच.
The बाद `` मानक Babylonian '' संस्करण dates from the 13th to the 10th centuries bc और bears the incipit शा naqba īmuru ( `` He जो देखी the गहन '' ).
fragments of approximately two तिहाई of this longer, twelve-tablet version have been बरामद.
कुछ of the best copies यहूद खोजा in the library ruins of the 7th-century bc assyrian किंग Ashurbanipal.
the स्टोरी centers on a दोस्ती between gilgamesh और enkidu.
enkidu is a जंगली man निर्मित by the देवताओं as gilgamesh 's बराबर to distract him इससे oppressing the लोगों of Uruk.
साथ, they journey to the Cedar Mountain to शिकस्त humbaba, its monstrous संरक्षक.
बाद they मार the सांड of स्वर्ग, which the goddess Ishtar भेजना to punish gilgamesh लिये spurning उसके अग्रिम.
as a दंड लिये these क्रियाएँ, the देवताओं वाक्य Enkidu to मौत.
The second हाफ of the epic focuses on gilgamesh 's तकलीफ at Enkidu 's मौत, and उसके क्वेस्ट for immortality.
In अनुक्रम to सीख the secret of अनन्त life, gilgamesh undertakes a long और perilous यात्रा.
he learns कि `` the जीवन that you are seeking you होगा never ढूँढें.
जब the gods created man they आवंटित to him death, but life वे retained in उनके अपना keeping. ''
इस quote was originally attributed to siduri in the बूढ़ा babylonian संस्करण of the एपिक, और then attributed to the अमर बाढ़ नायिका utnapishtim in the अक्कादी संस्करण of the एपिक.
nevertheless, gilgamesh 's कीर्ति जिया on बाद उसके मौत, क्युकी of उसके ग्रेट भवन प्रोजेक्ट, और his खाता of कया Utnapishtim बताई उसे happened दौरान the flood.
the स्टोरी रै महरूम अनूदित into अनेक different languages, and gilgamesh रै चूंकि become adapted in works of लोकप्रिय fiction.
A सुकेन्द्रिक ( or ) is an organism जिनकी cells contain complex structures enclosed भीतर झिल्लियों.
eukaryotes may अधिक formally be referred to as the टैक्सोन eukarya or eukaryota.
the defining membrane-bound ढांचा कि sets eukaryotic कोशिकाएं apart from prokaryotic कोशिकाएं is the केंद्रक, or नाभिकीय लिफाफा, भीतर which the जेनेटिक सामग्री is carried.
The उपस्थिति of a केंद्रक देता eukaryotes their name, जिससे comes इससे the Greek ( eu, `` good '' ) and ( karyon, `` nut '' or `` कर्नेल '' ).
Most eukaryotic cells also contain अन्य membrane-bound organelles such as mitochondria, chloroplasts और the golgi apparatus.
All विशाल जटिल जीवों are eukaryotes, सहित animals, पौधे और fungi.
the समूह also शामिल अनेक unicellular जीवों.
कोशिका प्रभाग in eukaryotes is अलग from that in organisms बगैर a केंद्रक ( prokaryote ).
it involves separating the duplicated गुणसूत्रों, through movements directed by microtubules.
वहीँ हैं दो प्रकार of प्रभाग processes.
In समसूत्रण, one कोशिका divides to उपज two genetically identical कोशिकाएं.
in meiosis, which is जरूरी in यौन जनन, one diploid कोशिका ( having दो उदाहरण of प्रत्येक chromosome, एक from each जनक ) undergoes recombination of प्रत्येक जोड़ी of parental गुणसूत्रों, और तब दो stages of कोशिका division, resulting in four अगुणित cells ( गैमीट ).
प्रत्येक gamete रै बस एक complement of गुणसूत्रों, प्रत्येक a अद्वितीय मिक्सर of the corresponding जोड़ी of parental chromosomes.
eukaryota appears to be monophyletic, और so makes up एक of the three domains of जीवन.
the दो other डोमेन, Bacteria and Archaea, हैं prokaryotes and have none of the above features.
Eukaryotes represent a tiny अल्पसंख्यक of all living बाते ; even in a human देह वहीँ हैं 10 टाइम्स more microbes than इंसान cells.
However, due to their much larger आकार their collective worldwide biomass is estimated at परिचय equal to कि of prokaryotes.
वे हैं माना to have first developed लगभग 1.6–2.1 billion सालो ago.
the उपयोग of अंतरजाल सेवाएं or तन्त्र साथ Internet अभिगम to defraud victims or to वरना take advantage of उन्हें, लिये example by stealing personal information, which can भी सीसे to identity चोरी.
a बहुत common रूप of अंतरजाल धोखाधड़ी is the वितरण of दुष्ट सुरक्षा तन्त्र.
Internet services can be प्रयुक्त to उपस्थित बेईमान solicitations to prospective victims, to conduct fraudulent ट्रांजेक्शन, or to संचारण the proceeds of धोखाधड़ी to वित्तीय संस्थानों or to अन्य connected साथ the scheme.
अंतरजाल धोखाधड़ी can occur in गपशप कक्ष, email, संदेश boards, or on वेबसाइटों.
the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Security सहायता Force ( isaf ) is a NATO -led सुरक्षा mission in अफगानिस्तान कि थी स्थापित by the संयुक्त राष्ट्र सुरक्षा Council in दिसम्बर 2001 by Resolution 1386, as envisaged by the Bonn Agreement.
इसके प्रमुख purpose is to ट्रैन the Afghan National Security शक्तियां ( ANSF ) and assist Afghanistan in पुनर्निर्माण कुंजी सरकारी institutions but is भी सगाई in the 2001-present युद्ध साथ बागी समूह.
ISAF was initially charged साथ securing Kabul and surrounding areas इससे the तालिबान, al Qaeda and factional warlords, so as to allow for the स्थापना of the Afghan Transitional प्रशासन headed by हामिद Karzai.
in October 2003, the un Security परिषद प्राधिकृत the विस्तार of the isaf mission throughout Afghanistan, और ISAF subsequently विस्तारित the मिशन in चार main stages over the whole of the देश.
इससे 2006 to 2011, ISAF था महरूम involved in increasingly अधिक intensive कॉम्बैट operations in दक्षिणी और पूर्वी Afghanistan.

कोका ( benzoylmethylecgonine ) ( INN ) is a crystalline tropane एल्कलॉएड कि is obtained इससे the पत्ते of the कोका संयंत्र.
The name आता इससे `` coca '' and the alkaloid प्रत्यय -ine, forming कोका.
it is a stimulant, an भूख suppressant, and a topical anesthetic.
Biologically, कोका acts as a serotonin–norepinephrine–dopamine reuptake inhibitor, भी ज्ञात as a ट्रिपल reuptake inhibitor ( TRI ).
It is addictive because of इसके प्रभाव on the mesolimbic बदला pathway.
नापसंद सबसे अणुओं, कोका रै pockets साथ दोनो ऊँची hydrophilic and lipophilic दक्षता, violating the rule of hydrophilic-lipophilic balance.
इस causes it to cross the blood–brain अवरोध far बेहतर than अन्य psychoactive रसायन and may even induce blood-brain अवरोध breakdown.
it is illegal to possess, produce, or वितरित कोका for non-medicinal and non-government-sanctioned purposes in लगभग प्रत्येक देश.

the स्पीकर of the United राज्य हाउस of प्रतिनिधि ( or स्पीकर of the हाउस ) is the पीठासीन अधिकारी of the कक्ष.
the दफ्तर थी established in 1789 by Article i, खण्ड 2 of the संयुक्त States Constitution, जिससे राज्य in भाग, `` The हाउस of प्रतिनिधि shall chuse उनके Speaker... ''
The वर्तमान स्पीकर is जॉन Boehner, a रिपब्लिकन who represents ओहियो 's 8th congressional district.

a लोलक is a वज़न निलंबित इससे a so कि it can swing freely.
जब a pendulum is displaced sideways from its resting equilibrium स्थिति, it is subject to a restoring फ़ोर्स due to गम्भीरता that will accelerate it back toward the संतुलन position.
जब released, the restoring force संयुक्त with the लोलक 's mass कल्याणकारी it to oscillate about the संतुलन स्थिति, सुहाने back और forth.
The समय लिये one पूरा cycle, a बाएँ swing and a सही swing, is पुकारा the काल.
a pendulum swings with a specific काल जिससे depends ( मुख्यतः ) on its लंबाई.
इससे इसके डिस्कवरी around 1602 by गैलीलियो गैलिली the नियमित गति of pendulums थी प्रयुक्त for timekeeping, और was the संसार 's सबसे सटीक timekeeping प्रौद्योगिकी जबतक the 1930s.
pendulums are प्रयुक्त to विनियमित लोलक घड़ियाँ, और हैं प्रयुक्त in scientific instruments ऐसे as accelerometers और seismometers.
historically they यहूद प्रयुक्त as gravimeters to measure the त्वरण of gravity in geophysical surveys, और भी as a standard of लंबाई.
the word 'pendulum ' is नई लैटिन, इससे the लैटिन pendulus, अर्थ 'टहलतेg '.
The simple gravity pendulum is an idealized गणितीय मॉडल of a लोलक.
This is a वज़न ( or bob ) on the समाप्त of a massless cord निलंबित from a, बगैर घर्षण.
जब दिए an आरंभिक push, it होगा झूले वापस और forth at a निरंतर आयाम.
रियल pendulums हैं विषय to घर्षण और एयर खीचें, so the आयाम of उनके swings गिरावट.
the First Battle of Bull चलाएं, भी ज्ञात as पहला manassas ( the नाम प्रयुक्त by confederate शक्तियां ), थी लड़ा on जुलाई 21, 1861, in प्रिंस विलियम County, वर्जिनिया, near the नगर of Manassas.
it was the पहला प्रमुख land बैटल of the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध.
बस months बाद the start of the युद्ध at Fort Sumter, the उत्तरी पब्लिक clamored for a कूच विरूद्ध the confederate पूंजी of Richmond, Virginia, which they expected to bring an जल्दी end to the विद्रोह.
yielding to राजनैतिक pressure, ब्रिगेडियर. Gen. irvin mcdowell led उसके unseasoned संघ फौज आरपार Bull चलाएं against the बराबर inexperienced confederate Army of ब्रिगेडियर. gen. P. G. T. beauregard camped near manassas जंक्शन.
McDowell 's महत्वाकांक्षी plan लिये a आश्चर्य flank attack on the Confederate बाएँ थी poorly चलाया by उसके officers and मेन ; nevertheless, the Confederates, जो था been नियोजन to आक्रमण the संघ left flank, मिला themselves at an initial disadvantage.
Confederate सुदृढीकरण अंतर्गत ब्रिगेडियर. gen. Joseph E. Johnston arrived from the Shenandoah घाटी by railroad and the course of the बैटल quickly बदला.
a brigade of Virginians under a relatively unknown कर्नल from the वर्जिनिया सैन्य Institute, थामस J. जैक्सन, stood their ground और जैक्सन received उसके famous nickname, `` stonewall Jackson ''.
the Confederates तब launched a strong counterattack, and as the Union troops began withdrawing अंतर्गत आग, many panicked और it turned into a rout as McDowell 's men frantically ran without अनुक्रम in the दिशा of वॉशिंगटन, D.C.
दोनो armies were sobered by the fierce fighting and अनेक casualties, और एहसास the युद्ध थी going to be much longer और bloodier than either था anticipated.

मौसम is the राज्य of the माहौल, to the degree that it is hot or ठंडा, गीला or शुष्क, शांत or stormy, clear or cloudy.
सबसे मौसम phenomena occur in the क्षोभमण्डल, बस नीचे the stratosphere.
मौसम generally refers to day-to-day temperature और वर्षण कार्यकलाप, whereas जलवायु is the पद लिये the औसत वायुमंडलीय शर्तें over longer periods of time.
When used बगैर qualification, `` मौसम '' is समझा to be the मौसम of धरती.
मौसम is चलित by air दबाव ( temperature और नमी ) मतभेद between one place and another.
These pressure और तापमान मतभेद can occur due to the sun कोण at any particular स्पॉट, जिससे varies by latitude इससे the ऊष्णकटिबन्ध.
the strong तापमान कंट्रास्ट between ध्रुवीय and tropical air gives वृद्धि to the जेट स्ट्रीम.
मौसम systems in the mid-latitudes, such as extratropical cyclones, are caused by instabilities of the jet stream प्रवाह.
Because the धरती 's axis is tilted relative to इसके कक्षीय प्लेन, धूप is घटना at अलग angles at different times of the year.
on Earth 's सतह, temperatures प्रायः दायरा ±40 °C ( −40 °F to 100 °F ) annually.
Over thousands of सालो, परिवर्तन in धरती 's orbit affect the amount और वितरण of सौर उर्जा प्राप्त by the धरती and influence long-term climate and वैश्विक जलवायु change.
Surface तापमान मतभेद in फेरे कारण pressure differences.
Higher altitudes हैं कूलर than lower altitudes due to मतभेद in compressional हीटिंग.
मौसम forecasting is the अनुप्रयोग of विज्ञान and technology to भविष्यवाणी the state of the माहौल for a भविष्य समय and a दिए स्थान.
The atmosphere is a chaotic system, so small परिवर्तन to एक part of the प्रणाली can grow to have large effects on the system as a whole.
Human attempts to कंट्रोल the weather have occurred throughout human history, and वहीँ is evidence कि इंसान कार्यकलाप such as कृषि and industry रै inadvertently modified weather patterns.
Studying कैसा the मौसम works on अन्य ग्रह has been helpful in समझना कैसा मौसम works on Earth.
A famous लैंडमार्क in the Solar प्रणाली, बृहस्पति 's ग्रेट रेड स्पॉट, is an anticyclonic storm ज्ञात to have existed for at least 300 years.
However, मौसम is not सीमित to planetary लाशें.
a स्टार 's corona is constantly being खोया to space, बनाना कया is essentially a very पतला atmosphere throughout the सौर प्रणाली.
the movement of mass ejected इससे the सूर्य is ज्ञात as the सौर wind.

In अनेक countries अंग्रेज़ी is the dominant language, लकिन करता not have official औकात.

अनेक of ये देशों are वर्तमान or former colonies or dependencies of the United किंगडम ( देखिए भी British Empire ), or of the United राज्य, itself a former colony of the uk.
notable अपवाद include रवांडा, जिससे was a पूर्व Belgian उपनिवेश और इरित्रिया, जिससे थी an इतालवी colony जहाँ the अंग्रेजों साम्राज्य spanned its कंट्रोल only in संसार युद्ध II और shortly after ( 1941-1952 ).
इण्डिया 's भाषाई चित्र is जटिल.
according to the Constitution of इण्डिया, `` हिंदी in the देवनागरी स्क्रिप्ट '' is the आधिकारिक भाषा of the संघ ; और अंग्रेज़ी the 'subsidiary आधिकारिक भाषा ' ; however, English is mandated लिये the authoritative ग्रन्थ of सब संघीय कानून और परम् Court decisions और ( साथ साथ Hindi ) is एक of the two भाषाएं of the Indian Parliament.

Southern कोन (, ) is a geographic प्रदेश रचित of the southernmost areas of South America, दक्षिण of the tropic of Capricorn.
हालांकि geographically इस includes दक्षिणी और भाग of Southeast ( são Paulo ) of Brazil, in शर्तें of political भूगोल the दक्षिणी कोन has traditionally comprised Argentina, Chile, पैराग्वे, और उरुग्वे.
in the narrowest भाव, it तभी कवर अर्जेंटीना, चिली और Uruguay, bounded on the उत्तर by the states of Brazil, पैराग्वे, Bolivia and पेरू, on the वेस्ट by the प्रशांत Ocean, और दक्षिण to the जंक्शन between the प्रशांत और अटलांटिक महासागर, जिससे it is the closest महाद्वीपीय area of अंटार्कटिक ( 1000 km ).
ऊँची जीवन प्रत्याशा, the उच्चतम इंसान विकास अनुक्रमणिका of लैटिन अमेरिका, ऊँची मानक of जीना, significant भागीदारी in the global markets and the उभरते अर्थव्यवस्था of its सदस्यों make the Southern कोन the सबसे prosperous macro-region in South अमेरिका.

बैठक हैं sometimes आयोजित around सम्मेलन tables.
in a meeting, two or more people आइये साथ to discuss एक or अधिक topics, often in a औपचारिक सेटिंग.
an आधिकारिक खेल in baseball, भी sometimes called a regulation game, is a game कि रै progressed परे the point at जिससे it can be considered complete if जरुरी.
इस is approximately the halfway point of the खेल.
in the मामला of inclement मौसम, any खेल जिससे रै पहुँचे this point may be रोका and shortened as needed, with the परिणाम होने फाइनल, और सब रिकॉर्ड और statistics गिने.
A खेल which has not पहुँचे इस point before होने रोका is either माना a suspended खेल ( to be जारी at a बाद तिथि इससे the पाइंट of stoppage ), or is simply रद्द और replayed इससे the प्रारंभ.
( इस depends on the नियम of each व्यक्तिगत league. )
in either मामला, no आंकडे हैं गिने जबतक the game becomes आधिकारिक.
Since सबसे पेशेवर बेसबॉल games are नौ पारी long, the पांचवां inning is used as the threshold for an आधिकारिक खेल.
if the visiting team is अग्रणी, or the खेल is tied, the end of the fifth inning marks this पाइंट.
if the home team ( जिससे bats पिछला ) is already ahead in the स्कोर, और theoretically होता नहीं need इसके हाफ of the fifth inning, तब 41⁄2 innings ( i.e., the middle of the fifth ) is माना an आधिकारिक खेल.
The खेल is also माना official if the घर टोली स्कोर to लो the सीसे in the नीचे of the पांचवां inning, since the खेल होता समाप्त immediately if the वही thing happened in the ninth.
in nearly सब मामले, the `` official game '' औकात is प्रयुक्त to determine whether a rain जाँच will be सम्मानित लिये प्रशंसक holding tickets.
if a game is started लकिन करता not reach the पाइंट of बनने official, प्रशंसक हैं हकदार to a new टिकट लिये the make-up खेल or ( in सबसे मामले ) any other available खेल of उनके चुनाव.
if a खेल is halted after it becomes आधिकारिक, the खेल is simply shortened और no बरसात जाँच is given.
the `` आधिकारिक खेल '' statistic received some attention दौरान the 1995 season, जब कैलोरी ripken, Jr. was approaching the रिकार्ड लिये लगातार games निभाई, previously held by Lou Gehrig.
Large संख्याएँ were लटका on the पक्ष of the b & O Warehouse at oriole Park at camden Yards to show the क्रमांक of games in Ripken 's streak.
प्रत्येक day, a new number was unfurled दौरान the पांचवां inning after प्रत्येक game had become official ( चूंकि the statistic would not have गिने if the खेल था महरूम रोका पहले कि पाइंट ).
A similar practice रै महरूम used to गिनती down toward the demolition of अनेक स्टेडियम ( सहित दिग्गजों Stadium in Philadelphia in 2003, Busch Memorial स्टेडियम in St. Louis in 2005, और the असली यांकी Stadium and Shea Stadium in नई यॉर्क नगर in 2008 ) ; as each खेल became official, the टोली would unveil a new ( lower ) क्रमांक showing the number of खेल left to be played in the stadium.
A टेलीफोन क्रमांक or phone क्रमांक is a sequence of अंक used to call from one टेलीफोन line to another in a public switched telephone संजाल.
जब टेलीफोन संख्याएँ यहूद invented, वे यहूद छोटी — as few as एक, two or three digits — and were दिए orally to a switchboard ऑपरेटर.
as phone प्रणालियों have grown और interconnected to encompass the संसार, telephone संख्याएँ have become longer.
In जोड to telephones, they now अभिगम other devices, such as कंप्यूटर and फैक्स मशीने.
the number contains the सूचना जरुरी to पहचानो uniquely the intended endpoint for the telephone call.
प्रत्येक ऐसे endpoint must have a अद्वितीय क्रमांक भीतर the पब्लिक switched टेलीफोन संजाल.
सबसे countries उपयोग फिक्स्ड length संख्याएँ ( for सामान्य लाइनों at least ) and इसलिए the number of endpoints determines the जरुरी length of the टेलीफोन क्रमांक.
it is also संभावित लिये each subscriber to have a नियत of shorter numbers लिये the endpoints सबसे प्रायः प्रयुक्त.
ये `` आशुलिपि '' or `` गति कॉलिंग '' संख्याएँ हैं automatically translated to unique टेलीफोन संख्याएँ before the call can be connected.
कुछ special सेवाएं have उनके own छोटी संख्याएँ ( e.g., 1-1-9, 9-1-1, 0-0-0, 9-9-9, 1-1-1, और 1-1-2 being the आपात सेवाएं संख्याएँ लिये चीन, Japan, South कोरियाई, ताईवान और Sri लंका ; Canada and the संयुक्त States ; ऑस्ट्रेलिया ; the संयुक्त किंगडम, आयरलैंड, दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी, कैंडल, Saudi अरब, the United अरब अमीरात, मोरक्को, मकाओ, Bahrain, क़तर, बांग्लादेश, Botswana, घाना, Kenya, Hong काँग, मलेशिया, मॉरीशस, सिंगापुर, ज़िम्बाब्वे, Trinidad, टोबैगो ; New जीलैंड ; Kuwait और the यूरोपीय Union, respectively. )
अनेक systems also allow काल्स भीतर a local क्षेत्रफल to be made बगैर डायलिंग the लोकल क्षेत्रफल code.
लिये example, a phone number in North America होगा start साथ तीन numbers ( ऐसे as 661 ), जिससे is the क्षेत्रफल code, followed by seven digits split into sections of three and चार ( ऐसे as 550-1212 ), which is the local क्रमांक.
कुछ क्षेत्रों अभी have mandatory ten-digit डायलिंग in place, even for लोकल calls.
Most टेलीफोन संजाल आज ( exceptions होने निजी intercom और सुरक्षित फोन networks ) हैं interconnected in the international टेलीफोन संजाल, where the स्वरूप of टेलीफोन संख्याएँ is मानकीकृत by ITU-T in the recommendation E.164.
This specifies कि the entire number चाहिए be 15 अंक or shorter, and शुरू with a country उपसर्ग.
लिये सबसे countries, this is followed by an area code or city code और the सदस्य क्रमांक, जिससे might consist of the कोड लिये a particular टेलीफोन exchange.
ITU-T अनुशंसा e.123 describes कैसा to represent an international टेलीफोन number in writing or छपाई, starting साथ a प्लस sign ( `` + '' ) और the देश code.
जब कॉलिंग an अंतरराष्ट्रीय क्रमांक इससे a फिक्स्ड लकीर phone, the + must be replaced with the international call उपसर्ग चुनी by the देश the call is being made from.
कुछ mobile फोन allow the + to be डाला directly.
The स्वरूप और आवंटन of लोकल phone numbers are नियंत्रित by each nation 's संबंधित सरकारी, either सीधे or by प्रायोजित संगठन ( such as nanpa overseen by neustar inc. ).
पहले a टेलीफोन कॉल is connected, the टेलीफोन क्रमांक जरूर be dialed by the कॉलिंग party or कॉलर.
the called party might have उपकरण कि presents कॉलर id पहले the कॉल is answered.
a संग्रहण agency is a business that pursues भुगतान of debts owed by individuals or businesses.
Most संग्रहण एजेंसियों operate as agents of लेनदारों और collect debts लिये a शुल्क or percentage of the कुल amount owed.
There हैं many types of संग्रहण agencies.
first-party एजेंसियों हैं oftentimes subsidiaries of the असली company the debt is owed to.
third-party एजेंसियों हैं पृथक companies contracted by a कम्पनी to collect debts on उनके निमित्त लिये a fee.
Debt buyers खरीदें the debt at a percentage of इसके value, तब attempt to collect it.
प्रत्येक country रै its own नियम और regulations regarding उन्हें.
Cannabis पुष्प साथ दृश्य trichomes
कैनबिस, also ज्ञात as मारिजुआना ( इससे the Mexican स्पेनी marihuana ), and by अन्य names, is a preparation of the कैनबिस संयंत्र intended लिये use as a psychoactive ड्रग and as medicine.
pharmacologically, the principal psychoactive constituent of cannabis is tetrahydrocannabinol ( THC ) ; it is एक of 483 ज्ञात compounds in the संयंत्र, सहित at least 84 अन्य cannabinoids, such as cannabidiol ( CBD ), cannabinol ( CBN ), tetrahydrocannabivarin ( thcv ).
और cannabigerol ( cbg ).
इस is a सूची of American football quarterbacks who have प्रारंभ for the वॉशिंगटन redskins, as well as इसके पूर्ववर्तियों the बोस्टन braves ( 1932 ) और Boston Redskins ( 1933 – 1936 ), in the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल League ( NFL ).
the वॉशिंगटन redskins franchise थी originally founded in Boston, मैसाचुसेट्स as the बोस्टन braves, नामित after the लोकल बेसबॉल मताधिकार.
The नाम was changed the following year to the Redskins.
In 1937, the franchise स्थानांतरित to वॉशिंगटन, d.c.

1st Special Forces Operational detachment-delta ( 1st SFOD-D ), popularly known as डेल्टा फ़ोर्स, is एक of the संयुक्त States ' four गुपचुप tier-one counter-terrorism and खास मिशन Units.
it थी formerly सूचीबद्ध as the Combat Applications Group by the विभाग of रक्षा लकिन has चूंकि महरूम officially re-designated the फौज compartmented Elements ( इक्का ).
While 1st sfod-d is administratively समर्थित by usasoc, it जलप्रपात under the operational कंट्रोल of the Joint खास परिचालन Command.
डेल्टा फ़ोर्स और इसके नेवी counterpart, the Naval Special warfare विकास Group, are the संयुक्त राज्य सैन्य 's प्राथमिक counter-terrorism इकाई.
Delta Force 's प्राथमिक कार्य हैं counter-terrorism, सीधा कार्रवाई, and नेशनल हस्तक्षेप operations, हालांकि it is an अत्यधिक बहुमुखी group capable of conducting अनेक प्रकार of covert मिशन, including, लकिन नहीं limited to, बंधक छुटकारा and छापे.
the सेंट्रल प्रज्ञा एजेंसी 's अत्यधिक secretive खास क्रियाएँ प्रभाग ( उदास ) and अधिक specifically its elite Special Operations समूह ( sog ) often works with – और recruits – operators इससे डेल्टा Force.
Alpha क्षय is एक example प्रकार of रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय, in जिससे an परमाणु केंद्रक emits an अल्फा कण, और thereby transforms ( or 'क्षयs ' ) into an अणु साथ a द्रव्यमान क्रमांक 4 कम और atomic क्रमांक 2 कम.
अनेक other types of decays हैं संभावित.
Radioactive decay, भी ज्ञात as नाभिकीय क्षय or radioactivity, is the प्रक्रम by which a nucleus of an unstable atom loses उर्जा by emitting particles of आयनकारी विकिरण.
A सामग्री कि अनायास emits इस kind of radiation — which शामिल the उत्सर्जन of ऊर्जावान alpha अणु, बीटा अणु, and गामा किरणें — is माना radioactive.
वहीँ are अनेक अलग प्रकार of रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय ( see table below ).
a क्षय, or loss of energy, परिणाम when an अणु साथ one प्रकार of केंद्रक, पुकारा the जनक radionuclide, transforms to an atom with a केंद्रक in a अलग राज्य, or to a अलग nucleus containing अलग numbers of protons और neutrons.
either of ये उत्पाद is named the बेटी nuclide.
In कुछ decays the जनक और बेटी are अलग रासायनिक elements, and यूँ the क्षय प्रक्रम परिणाम in नाभिकीय transmutation ( सृष्टि of an अणु of a नई तत्व ).
The पहला decay प्रक्रियाओं to be discovered यहूद अल्फा क्षय, beta decay, और गामा decay.
अल्फा क्षय occurs when the केंद्रक ejects an अल्फा कण ( हीलियम nucleus ).
इस is the most common प्रक्रम of emitting nucleons, लकिन in rarer types of decays, nuclei can eject protons, or विशिष्ट nuclei of other तत्व ( in the process called क्लस्टर क्षय ).
बीटा decay occurs जब the nucleus emits an इलेक्ट्रॉन or positron और a type of neutrino, in a प्रक्रम that परिवर्तन a प्रोटॉन to a neutron or the अन्य रास्ता around.
The केंद्रक may capture an orbiting इलेक्ट्रॉन, converting a प्रोटॉन into a न्यूट्रॉन ( electron कैप्चर ).
सब of these प्रक्रियाओं परिणाम in nuclear transmutation.
by contrast, वहीँ exist रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय प्रक्रियाओं कि do नहीं result in transmutation.
the energy of an उत्साहित केंद्रक may be emitted as a gamma रे in gamma decay, or used to eject an कक्षीय इलेक्ट्रॉन by बातचीत with the उत्साहित nucleus in a प्रक्रम called आतंरिक परिवर्तन.
radioisotopes occasionally emit neutrons, और इस परिणाम in a बदलें in an तत्व from एक समस्थानिक to another.
एक type of रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय results in उत्पाद जिससे are नहीं पारिभाषित, लकिन appear in a दायरा of `` pieces '' of the असली केंद्रक.
This क्षय is पुकारा spontaneous fission.
This क्षय happens जब a large अस्थिर केंद्रक अनायास splits into दो ( and occasionally तीन ) छोटी बेटी nuclei, and प्रायः emits गामा rays, neutrons, or other particles as a consequence.
रेडियोसक्रिय decay is a stochastic ( i.e., यादृच्छिक ) प्रक्रम at the level of single अणु, in कि, according to क्वांटम theory, it is impossible to predict when a particular atom will क्षय.
However, the मौका that a दिए अणु will क्षय is constant over समय.
लिये a large क्रमांक of atoms, the decay rate for the संग्रहण is computable इससे the measured decay स्थिरांक of the nuclides ( or equivalently इससे the half-lifes ).
वैक्सिंग is a रूप of semi-permanent hair removal जिससे removes the बाल इससे the root.
नई बाल होगा नहीं grow back in the previously waxed क्षेत्रफल लिये दो to eight सप्ताह, हालांकि कुछ लोगों होगा प्रारंभ to देखिए regrowth in only a week.
Almost कोई क्षेत्रफल of the देह can be waxed, including eyebrows, फेस, बिकिनी क्षेत्रफल, legs, बाहें, वापस, abdomen and feet.
वहीँ हैं many प्रकार of वैक्सिंग suitable लिये निकालना unwanted बाल.
Strip वैक्सिंग is संपन्नता by spreading a wax thinly over the skin.
A cloth or पेपर strip is then pressed on the शीर्ष and ripped off the दिशा of बाल growth.
इस removes the wax साथ with the बाल.
Strip wax can भी be बना at घर using lemon juice, water, sugar and मधु.
hot waxing utilizes Hot मोम ( as opposed to strip wax ).
in this मामला, the wax is लागू somewhat thickly और साथ no cloth or पेपर स्ट्रिप्स.
The wax तब hardens when it cools, यूँ allowing the easy removal by a चिकित्सक बगैर the सहायता of cloths.
This वैक्सिंग method is very फायदेमंद to लोगों जो have sensitive skin.

Ancient रोमन संस्कृति existed throughout the लगभग 1200-year इतिहास of the civilization of Ancient रोम.
the term refers to the संस्कृति of the Roman Republic, later the रोमन साम्राज्य, जिससे, at its शिखर, covered an area इससे lowland स्कॉटलैंड and मोरक्को to the euphrates.
जीवन in प्राचीन रोम revolved around the city of Rome, इसके famed सात पहाड़ियाँ, और its monumental structures ऐसे as the flavian amphitheatre ( अभी पुकारा the कोलोसियम ), the फ़ोरम of त्राजान, और the pantheon.
The city also था several थिएटर, gymnasiums, और many taverns, baths, and brothels.
Throughout the territory अंतर्गत प्राचीन Rome 's कंट्रोल, आवासीय वास्तुकला ranged from very modest घरों to country विला, and in the पूंजी city of Rome, there were imperial residences on the elegant palatine Hill, from जिससे the शब्द palace is derived.
The विशाल majority of the जनसांख्यिकी जिया in the नगर center, packed into insulae ( अपार्टमेंट ब्लॉक ).
The city of Rome थी the largest megalopolis of कि time, with a जनसांख्यिकी कि may खूब have exceeded one लाख लोगों, साथ a ऊँची end अनुमान of 3.6 लाख and a कम end estimate of 450,000.
ऐतिहासिक estimates indicate कि around 30 प्रतिशत of the जनसांख्यिकी अंतर्गत the city 's jurisdiction जिया in innumerable शहरी centers, साथ population of at तनिक 10,000 और अनेक सैन्य settlements, a बहुत ऊँची rate of urbanization by pre-industrial standards.
The most urbanized भाग of the साम्राज्य was इटली, जिससे था an estimated rate of शहरी of 32 %, the same रेट of urbanization of England in 1800.
सबसे Roman कस्बों and शहरों था a फ़ोरम, temples and the वही type of इमारतें, on a smaller स्केल, as मिला in Rome.
the large शहरी जनसांख्यिकी जरूरी an endless supply of food which थी a जटिल logistical task, सहित acquiring, transporting, storing और वितरण of खाना लिये Rome and अन्य urban centers.
इतालवी खेतो supplied सब्जियां and फल, लकिन मछली और meat were luxuries.
Aqueducts यहूद निर्मित to bring जल to urban centers and वाइन and आयल were आयातित इससे hispania, gaul and अफ़्रीकी.
There थी a very विशाल राशि of commerce between the प्रांतों of the रोमन साम्राज्य, since इसके परिवहन प्रौद्योगिकी was बहुत कुशल.
the औसत लागत of transport और the technology were comparable साथ 18th-century यूरोपीय.
the बाद city of रोम किया नहीं भरण the स्पेस भीतर इसके प्राचीन aurelian दीवारें until बाद 1870.
अस्सी percent of the जनसांख्यिकी अंतर्गत the क्षेत्राधिकार of ancient Rome जिया in the countryside in settlements with कम than 10 thousand inhabitants.
Landlords generally resided in शहरों and उनके estates were बाएँ in the परवाह of farm managers.
The plight of rural स्लेव थी generally बदतर than their counterparts working in urban वैभवशाली households.
to stimulate a उच्चतर labor productivity most जमींदार freed a large number of स्लेव and many प्राप्त मजदूरी.
Some records indicate कि `` as अनेक as 42 लोगों जिया in एक small फार्म हट in मिश्र, जबकि six families स्वामित्व a single olive tree. ''.
Such a ग्रामीण पर्यावरण continued to induce माइग्रेशन of population to शहरी centers जबतक the जल्दी 2nd सदी, जब the शहरी जनसांख्यिकी stopped growing and started to मनाही.
Starting in the मध्य of the 2nd सदी bc, private यूनानी संस्कृति was increasingly in ascendancy, in spite of tirades against the `` softening '' effects of Hellenized संस्कृति from the रूढ़िवादी moralists.
by the समय of augustus, cultured यूनानी household स्लेव taught the Roman young ( sometimes even the girls ) ; chefs, decorators, secretaries, doctors, और hairdressers—all आए from the यूनानी ईस्ट.
Greek sculptures adorned Hellenistic लैंडस्केप बागवानी on the Palatine or in the विला, or were imitated in रोमन sculpture गज by Greek slaves.
the Roman भोजन preserved in the cookery किताबे ascribed to Apicius is essentially यूनानी.
रोमन लेखक disdained लैटिन for a cultured यूनानी स्टाइल.
Only in विधि and शासन थी the Italic nature of Rome 's accretive culture supreme.
Against इस इंसान background, दोनो the शहरी and ग्रामीण सेटिंग, एक of इतिहास 's most influential सभ्यताओं took shape, leaving पीछे a cultural विरासत कि survives in भाग today.
James जोसेफ `` Duffy '' waldorf, Jr. ( born अगस्त 20, 1962 ) is an American पेशेवर मनःस्थिति.

Glass उत्पादन involves two main विधि – the फ्लैश glass प्रक्रम, which produces चादर कांच, और glassblowing जिससे produces bottles और other containers.
a ऋतु is a subdivision of the साल, चिह्नित by परिवर्तन in मौसम, पारिस्थितिकी, and घंटों of daylight.
Seasons result from the वार्षिक revolution of the Earth around the Sun and the झुकाव of the Earth 's axis सापेक्ष to the प्लेन of revolution.
In शीतोष्ण और polar regions, the सीज़न हैं चिह्नित by परिवर्तन in the तीव्रता of धूप कि पहुँच the धरती 's सतह, विसंगतियाँ of which may कारण animals to go into hibernation or to migrate, और plants to be dormant.
दौरान may, June and जुलाई, the उत्तरी गोलार्ध is exposed to अधिक direct धूप क्युकी the hemisphere चेहरों the सूर्य.
the same is सच्चा of the southern hemisphere in नवम्बर, December and January.
It is the झुकाव of the धरती that causes the सूर्य to be higher in the आसमान दौरान the summer महीने जिससे increases the solar फ्लक्स.
However, due to मौसमी lag, जून, July and अगस्त हैं the hottest months in the उत्तरी hemisphere and December, January और फ़रवरी हैं the hottest months in the दक्षिणी गोलार्ध.
in शीतोष्ण और subpolar regions, generally four पंचांग -based सीज़न ( साथ उनके adjectives ) are पहचाना : spring ( vernal ), गर्मियाँ ( estival ), पतझड़ ( autumnal ) और winter ( hibernal ).
however, ecologists ज़्यादातर use a six season model लिये शीतोष्ण जलवायु regions कि शामिल pre-spring ( prevernal ) और late summer ( serotinal ) as पृथक सीज़न साथ साथ the परंपरागत चार.
hot regions have two or three सीज़न ; the बरसात ( or wet, or monsoon ) season और the dry ऋतु, and in some तीव्र क्षेत्रों, a कूल or mild season.
in some parts of the world, special `` सीज़न '' are loosely पारिभाषित आधारित on important कार्यक्रम ऐसे as a hurricane season, tornado season or a दावानल season.

the बैटल of Fort sumter ( अप्रैल 12–14, 1861 ) was the bombardment और आत्मसमर्पण of Fort Sumter, निकट Charleston, दक्षिण कैरोलिना, कि प्रारंभ the अमरीकी सिविल War.
Following घोषणाओं of secession by सात Southern राज्य, दक्षिण Carolina demanded कि the U.S. फौज लापरवाही its facilities in Charleston हार्बर.
on December 26, 1860, U.S. प्रमुख Robert Anderson surreptitiously स्थानांतरित उसके छोटी command from the indefensible फोर्ट Moultrie on सुलीवान 's Island to Fort Sumter, a substantial किला controlling the प्रवेश of चार्ल्सटन Harbor.
an attempt by U.S. अध्यक्ष James Buchanan to reinforce और resupply एंडरसन, using the निहत्थे व्यापारी ship स्टार of the वेस्ट, failed when it was fired upon by shore बैटरी on जनवरी 9, 1861.
दक्षिण कैरोलिना अधिकारियों then जब्त सब संघीय property in the चार्ल्सटन area, except for फोर्ट Sumter.
During the जल्दी महीने of 1861, the हालात around Fort sumter increasingly began to resemble a siege.
in कूच, Brig. gen. P. G. T. Beauregard, the पहला सामान्य अधिकारी of the newly formed Confederate राज्य of America, थी placed in command of confederate शक्तियां in चार्ल्सटन.
Beauregard energetically directed the strengthening of batteries around Charleston harbor aimed at फोर्ट sumter.
शर्तें in the फोर्ट grew dire as the Union सैनिको rushed to पूरा the installation of अतिरिक्त बंदूकों.
Anderson थी छोटी of men, food, और आपूर्तियाँ.
The resupply of फोर्ट sumter became the पहला संकट of the administration of President अब्राहम Lincoln.
he notified the Governor of South Carolina, फ्रांसिस W. Pickens, कि he was sending सप्लाई जहाजों, जिससे resulted in an ultimatum इससे the Confederate government : evacuate फोर्ट sumter immediately.
प्रमुख Anderson refused to आत्मसमर्पण.
Beginning at 4:30 a.m. on April 12, the Confederates bombarded the फोर्ट इससे artillery batteries surrounding the हार्बर.
हालांकि the Union गैरीसन returned fire, वे यहूद significantly outgunned और, बाद 34 घंटों, प्रमुख Anderson सहमत to evacuate.
वहीँ थी no घाटा of life on either पक्ष as a सीधा परिणाम of इस सगाई, हालांकि a गन explosion during the आत्मसमर्पण ceremonies on अप्रैल 14 caused दो Union मौतों.
following the बैटल, वहीँ थी widespread support from दोनो उत्तर और दक्षिण for further सैन्य action.
lincoln 's immediate call for 75,000 volunteers to दबाने the विद्रोह resulted in an additional चार southern स्लेव states also declaring उनके secession और joining the confederacy.

3g, short लिये तीसरा पीढी, is the third generation of मोबाईल telecommunications प्रौद्योगिकी.
3g telecommunication संजाल support services कि provide an सूचना transfer rate of at तनिक 200 kbit/s.
however, अनेक सेवाएं advertised as 3G provide higher गति than the न्यूनतम तकनीकी requirements लिये a 3G service.
हाल 3g releases, often denoted 3.5G and 3.75g, also provide मोबाईल broadband access of several mbit/s to smartphones and मोबाईल modems in लैपटॉप computers.
3g finds application in बेतार आवाज़ telephony, मोबाईल अंतरजाल अभिगम, fixed wireless अंतरजाल अभिगम, वीडियो काल्स और mobile TV.

hepatitis C is an संक्रामक बीमारी affecting primarily the जिगर, caused by the hepatitis c virus ( HCV ).
The infection is प्रायः asymptomatic, लकिन दीर्घकालिक संक्रमण can सीसे to scarring of the जिगर and ultimately to cirrhosis, जिससे is generally apparent बाद many सालो.
in कुछ मामले, those साथ cirrhosis होगा go on to develop liver failure, जिगर कर्कट or life-threatening esophageal और gastric varices.
hcv is spread primarily by blood-to-blood सम्पर्क associated with intravenous drug उपयोग, poorly sterilized चिकित्सा equipment and transfusions.
An अनुमानित 130–200 million लोगों विश्वव्यापी हैं infected साथ.
The अस्तित्व of ( originally `` non- A non- b hepatitis '' ) was postulated in the 1970s और proven in 1989.
तभी infects इंसानो और chimpanzees.
the वायरस persists in the जिगर in परिचय 85 % of those संक्रमित.
इस persistent संक्रमण can be treated साथ दवा : the मानक therapy is a संयोजन of peginterferon and ribavirin, साथ either boceprevir or telaprevir added in कुछ cases.
overall, 50–80 % of लोगों treated are cured.
Those जो develop cirrhosis or जिगर कर्कट may आवश्यकता a liver transplant.
is the अग्रणी cause of liver प्रत्यारोपण, हालांकि the virus usually बारंबार बाद प्रत्यारोपण.
