A लचीली बिता खाता ( fsa ), भी ज्ञात as a flexible बिता arrangement, is एक of a क्रमांक of tax-advantaged वित्तीय खाते कि can be नियत up through a cafeteria योजना of an employer in the संयुक्त राज्य.
An fsa allows an कर्मचारी to नियत aside a portion of earnings to अदा लिये योग्य खर्च as स्थापित in the कैफेटेरिया योजना, सबसे commonly for चिकित्सा खर्च but often लिये निर्भर care or अन्य खर्च.
Money deducted from an कर्मचारी 's अदा into an fsa is नहीं विषय to payroll कर, resulting in substantial payroll tax बचत.
One significant disadvantage to using an FSA is कि निधि not प्रयुक्त by the समाप्त of the योजना year are खोया to the कर्मचारी, ज्ञात as the `` उपयोग it or खोना it '' rule.
the सबसे common type of लचीली बिता खाता, the medical expense FSA ( भी चिकित्सा fsa or health FSA ), is समान to a health बचत account ( HSA ) or a स्वास्थ्य reimbursement खाता ( hra ).
However, जबकि hsas और hras हैं लगभग exclusively used as components of a उपभोक्ता चलित health care योजना, medical FSAs हैं commonly offered with more traditional स्वास्थ्य plans as well.
in addition, निधि in a स्वास्थ्य savings account हैं नहीं lost when the योजना साल is over, unlike funds in an FSA.
Paper forms or an fsa डेबिट कार्ड, भी known as a flexcard, may be used to access the खाता funds.
टेनेसी ( ) ( ) is a u.S. राज्य located in the southeastern United राज्य.
Tennessee is the 36th most extensive and the 17th सबसे populous of the 50 United राज्य.
Tennessee is bordered by Kentucky और वर्जिनिया to the north, North कैरोलिना to the ईस्ट, जॉर्जिया, अलबामा, and Mississippi to the south, और अरकंसास और Missouri to the वेस्ट.
the Appalachian Mountains dominate the eastern भाग of the राज्य, and the मिसिसिपी River फ़ॉर्म the state 's पश्चिमी किनारा.
टेनेसी 's capital और दूसरी largest city is Nashville, which रै a population of 609,644.
Memphis is the राज्य 's largest नगर, with a population of 652,050.
The state of Tennessee is rooted in the Watauga संघ, a 1772 frontier अनुबंध generally regarded as the पहला संवैधानिक government वेस्ट of the Appalachians.
What is अभी टेनेसी थी initially part of उत्तर कैरोलिना, and बाद भाग of the Southwest Territory.
टेनेसी was admitted to the संघ as the 16th राज्य on जून 1, 1796.
टेनेसी थी the last राज्य to leave the Union and जुड़ें the confederacy at the outbreak of the u.S. Civil War in 1861, and the first state to be readmitted to the Union at the end of the युद्ध.
टेनेसी सुसज्जित अधिक सैनिको लिये the Confederate Army than कोई other राज्य, and more soldiers लिये the संघ फौज than कोई अन्य Southern राज्य.
in the 20th century, टेनेसी transitioned इससे an agrarian अर्थव्यवस्था to a more diversified अर्थव्यवस्था, aided at टाइम्स by संघीय entities such as the Tennessee घाटी Authority.
In the early 1940s, the city of ओक लकीरें थी स्थापित to हाउस the मैनहटन Project 's uranium संवर्धन facilities, helping to निर्माण the world 's first परमाणु bomb.
Tennessee has played a critical role in the development of अनेक फ़ॉर्म of अमरीकी लोकप्रिय म्यूज़िक, सहित rock और roll, ब्लूज़, country, और rockabilly.
beale गली in Memphis is माना by many to be the जन्मस्थान of the ब्लूज़, with musicians ऐसे as W.C. Handy performing in इसके clubs as early as 1909.
Memphis was also घर to Sun Records, जहाँ संगीतकारों ऐसे as एल्विस प्रेस्ली, इसहाक़ हेज़, जॉनी नकदी, कार्ल Perkins, Jerry ली लुईस, रॉय Orbison, और चार्ली समृद्ध began उनके recording करियर, और where rock और फेंकें took आकार in the 1950s.
the 1927 विक्टर रिकॉर्डिंग सत्र in Bristol generally mark the शुरूआत of the country music विधा और the वृद्धि of the ग्रैंड ओले opry in the 1930s helped मेक नैशविले the center of the country म्यूज़िक रिकॉर्डिंग उद्योग.
Three ईंटें और गारा museums recognize टेनेसी 's role in nurturing various forms of लोकप्रिय म्यूज़िक : the मेम्फिस चट्टान N ' Soul Museum, the देश म्यूज़िक Hall of Fame और Museum in Nashville, and the International rock-a-billy संग्रहालय in Jackson.
in addition, the Rockabilly Hall of कीर्ति, an ऑनलाइन साईट recognizing the विकास of rockabilly in जिससे टेनेसी निभाई a crucial भूमिका, is based in Nashville.
टेनेसी 's major industries include कृषि, निर्माण, और tourism.
Poultry, soybeans, और cattle हैं the state 's प्राथमिक agricultural products, and major निर्माण exports शामिल chemicals, परिवहन equipment, और विद्युत उपकरण.
the Great Smoky kyu नेशनल पार्क, the nation 's most visited नेशनल पार्क, is headquartered in the पूर्वी part of the state, and a खण्ड of the Appalachian Trail roughly फ़ॉलो the tennessee-north कैरोलिना किनारा.
अन्य major पर्यटक attractions include the टेनेसी एक्वेरियम in चट्टानूगा, the sunsphere in Knoxville, dollywood in कबूतर forge, the Parthenon, the Country Music Hall of कीर्ति and संग्रहालय, और Ryman Auditorium in Nashville, और एल्विस प्रेस्ली 's graceland निवास और मकबरा in मेम्फिस.

Major League Baseball ( MLB ) is a पेशेवर baseball लीग, consisting of टीमों कि play in the National लीग और the अमरीकी League.
डेटिंग to 1876 और 1901 respectively, the two leagues merged in 2000 into a सिंगल organization led by the कमिश्नर of बेसबॉल, बाद 100 years as पृथक विधिक entities.
MLB constitutes एक of the प्रमुख professional sports leagues of the United States और Canada.
It is composed of 30 टीमों — 29 in the United States और एक in कनाडा.
टीमों in एमएलबी खेल 162 games each season over छह महीने ( अप्रैल through सितंबर ).
Five टीमों in प्रत्येक league अग्रिम to a four-round postseason टूर्नामेंट that culminates in the संसार श्रेणी, a best-of-seven-games चैंपियनशिप series between the two लीग champions which तिथियाँ to 1903.
the संगठन oversees many minor-league बेसबॉल leagues which operate about 240 teams संबद्ध साथ the major-league क्लब.
साथ the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Baseball संघ, the league भी manages the अंतरराष्ट्रीय World बेसबॉल क्लासिक टूर्नामेंट.
MLB रै the highest ऋतु attendance of कोई खेल league in the world साथ nearly 75 लाख spectators in 2012.
डेलावेयर ( ) is a u.S. राज्य स्तिथ on the अटलांटिक coast in the mid-atlantic प्रदेश of the United राज्य.
It is bordered to the south और वेस्ट by Maryland, to the पूर्वोत्तर by नई Jersey, और to the उत्तर by पेन्सिलवेनिया.
the राज्य takes its नाम इससे Thomas West, 3rd सामन्त de La warr, an अंग्रेज़ी nobleman and वर्जिनिया 's पहला औपनिवेशिक governor, after जिसको कया is now पुकारा Cape Henlopen थी originally named.
Delaware is स्तिथ in the northeastern portion of the delmarva Peninsula और is the दूसरी smallest, the sixth least populous, लकिन the sixth सबसे densely आबादी of the पचास United States.
Delaware is विभाजित into three काउंटी.
From north to south, these three काउंटी हैं नई Castle, Kent, और Sussex.
जबकि the दक्षिणी दो काउंटी have historically been predominantly agricultural, नई Castle काउंटी has महरूम more industrialized.
पहले इसके तटरेखा was explored by europeans in the 16th सदी, Delaware was inhabited by अनेक समूह of Native अमेरिकी, including the lenape in the north और nanticoke in the दक्षिण.
it थी initially colonized by Dutch व्यापारियों at zwaanendael, located near the present कस्बा of Lewes, in 1631.
डेलावेयर was one of the 13 colonies participating in the American Revolution और on December 7, 1787, became the first राज्य to ratify the संविधान of the संयुक्त राज्य, thereby becoming ज्ञात as the First राज्य.
उर्जा परिवर्तन in उर्जा प्रणालियों भाषा
उर्जा परिवर्तन or energy परिवर्तन is the process of changing एक रूप of energy to another.
In भौतिकी, the term energy describes the क्षमता to produce निश्चित परिवर्तन within a system, बगैर लिहाज़ to सीमाएं in परिवर्तन imposed by एन्ट्रॉपी.
परिवर्तन in कुल उर्जा of प्रणालियों can तभी be संपन्नता by adding or subtracting energy from उन्हें, as energy is a मात्रा जिससे is conserved, according to the first विधि of ऊष्मागतिकी.
According to खास relativity, परिवर्तन in the energy of systems होगा also coincide with परिवर्तन in the प्रणाली 's mass, और the कुल राशि of mass of a system is a measure of इसके उर्जा.
Energy in a प्रणाली may be रूपांतरित so that it resides in a अलग राज्य, or a अलग type of उर्जा.
उर्जा in अनेक राज्य may be used to do अनेक किस्में of physical work.
उर्जा may be प्रयुक्त in प्राकृतिक प्रक्रियाओं or मशीने, or else to provide कुछ सेवा to समाज ( such as heat, light, or गति ).
For example, an आतंरिक combustion इंजन converts the potential chemical energy in गैसोलीन and ऑक्सीजन into ऊष्मा, जिससे is तब रूपांतरित into the propulsive उर्जा ( kinetic energy that चालें a गाडी ).
a solar cell converts सौर विकिरण into विद्युत energy that can then be used to light a bulb or power a कंप्यूटर.
The generic name for a यंत्र which converts उर्जा from एक form to another, is a ट्रान्सड्यूसर.
In सामान्य, सबसे types of energy, save लिये thermal energy, may be converted efficiently to कोई अन्य दयालु of energy.
sometimes this occurs with an दक्षता of essentially 100 %, ऐसे as when potential energy is परिवर्तित to गतिज energy as an object जलप्रपात in vacuum, or जब it orbits nearer or दूर from another object, in space.
परिवर्तन of other types of energies to heat may also occurs साथ nearly perfect दक्षता ( many types of घर्षण do this ).
अपवाद लिये पूर्ण परिवर्तन दक्षता ( even for पृथक systems ) occur जब उर्जा रै already महरूम partly distributed among अनेक available क्वांटम states लिये a संग्रहण of particles, which are freely अनुमत to explore कोई state of momentum और position ( phase स्पेस ).
in such हालातों, a माप पुकारा एन्ट्रॉपी, or evening-out of उर्जा वितरण in ऐसे states, dictates कि भविष्य states of the प्रणाली must be of at least equal evenness in energy distribution.
( वहीँ is no way, taking the universe as a whole, to collect energy into fewer states, एकबार it has स्प्रेड to उन्हें ).
A consequence of this आवश्यकता is that वहीँ are सीमाएं to the दक्षता साथ जिससे थर्मल उर्जा can be converted to other kinds of उर्जा, चूंकि thermal उर्जा in equilibrium at a दिए तापमान already represents the maximal evening-out of उर्जा between सब possible राज्य.
Such energy is sometimes माना `` degraded उर्जा, '' because it is not entirely usable.
the दूसरी law of ऊष्मागतिकी is a way of stating कि, लिये this कारण, थर्मल उर्जा in a प्रणाली may be converted to अन्य kinds of energy साथ efficiencies approaching 100 %, तभी if the entropy ( even-ness or विकार ) of the ब्रह्मांड is increased by other अर्थात्, to compensate for the घटी in entropy संबद्ध साथ the disappearance of the थर्मल energy और इसके एन्ट्रॉपी content.
वरना, तभी a भाग of thermal उर्जा may be converted to अन्य kinds of उर्जा ( और thus, उपयोगी कार्य ), since the शेष of the ऊष्मा जरूर be सुरक्षित to be transferred to a thermal reservoir at a lower तापमान, in ऐसे a way that the increase in Entropy लिये this process अधिक than compensates लिये the एन्ट्रॉपी घटी associated with परिवर्तन of the बाकी of the ऊष्मा into अन्य प्रकार of energy.
The नेशनल हॉकी लीग ( एनएचएल ; ) is an `` unincorporated not-for-profit संघ '' which operates a प्रमुख professional बर्फ hockey लीग of 30 franchised सदस्य क्लब, of जिससे seven हैं currently located in Canada और 23 in the United राज्य.
Headquartered in नई यॉर्क नगर, the NHL is widely considered to be the प्रीमियर पेशेवर ice हॉकी लीग in the world, and one of the major पेशेवर खेल leagues in the संयुक्त States and कनाडा.
The Stanley Cup, the oldest पेशेवर sports ट्रॉफी in उत्तर अमेरिका, is awarded annually to the लीग playoff champion at the समाप्त of प्रत्येक ऋतु.
the लीग थी organized on नवम्बर 26, 1917, in Montreal, क्यूबेक, कनाडा, बाद the suspension of operations of इसके पूर्ववर्ती संगठन, the नेशनल Hockey संघ ( NHA ), जिससे था महरूम संस्थापित in 1909.
it प्रारंभ साथ four टीमों and, through a series of expansions, contractions, and relocations, the league is now composed of 30 active franchises.

After a labour dispute कि led to the रद्दीकरण of the संपूर्ण 2004–05 ऋतु, the league resumed play अंतर्गत a नई collective bargaining अनुबंध कि included a salary cap.
In 2009, the NHL enjoyed रिकार्ड highs in शर्तें of sponsorships, attendance, और टेलीविज़न ऑडियंस.
the NHL draws many highly skilled खिलाड़ी इससे all over the world और फिलहाल रै खिलाड़ी from about 20 different देशों.
Although Canadians have historically गठित the majority of the खिलाड़ी in the एनएचएल, over the पास्ट four plus decades the percentages of US और यूरोपीय खिलाड़ी have increased both क्युकी of the एनएचएल 's continued विस्तार इससे six to thirty क्लब since 1967, और the increased उपलब्धता of अत्यधिक skilled यूरोपीय खिलाड़ी.
This is the complete list of the ratified और unratified amendments to the संयुक्त States संविधान which प्राप्त the स्वीकृति of the संयुक्त States कॉंग्रेस.
Twenty-seven amendments have been ratified since the असली हस्ताक्षर of the संविधान, the first टेन of which are known collectively as the विधेयक of अधिकारों.
the कार्यविधि for amending the संयुक्त States Constitution is governed by आलेख v of the असली टेक्स्ट.
There have been many अन्य प्रस्ताव लिये amendments to the United राज्य संविधान introduced in Congress, लकिन नहीं सुपुर्द to the states.
पहले an amendment can लो प्रभाव, it must be proposed to the states by a two-thirds vote of both घरों of Congress or by a सम्मेलन ( ज्ञात as an Article V convention ) पुकारा by two-thirds of the राज्य, और ratified by three-fourths of the states or by three-fourths of प्रथाओं thereof, the विधि of अनुसमर्थन होने determined by Congress at the time of proposal.
to date, no सम्मेलन लिये proposing amendments has महरूम called by the राज्य, और only once—in 1933 for the ratification of the twenty-first amendment —has the सम्मेलन method of अनुसमर्थन महरूम employed.
fmr llc ( वफ़ादारी प्रबन्धन और शोध ) or वफ़ादारी निवेश is an अमरीकी बहुराष्ट्रीय वित्तीय सेवाएं corporation.
It is एक of the largest mutual निधि और financial सेवाएं समूह in the संसार.
it was founded in 1946 और serves उत्तर अमरीकी investors.

Fidelity अंतरराष्ट्रीय सीमित ( फील ), was an अंतरराष्ट्रीय affiliate founded in 1969, सेवारत सबसे countries in the बाकी of the संसार.

Sociology is the वैज्ञानिक पढ़ाई of human society and इसके origins, development, संगठन, और संस्थानों.
It is a social science जिससे उपयोग various methods of empirical छानबीन और critical विश्लेषण to develop a body of knowledge परिचय इंसान social activity, structures, and functions.
A goal for many sociologists is to conduct शोध which may be लागू सीधे to सोशल policy and welfare, while अन्य फ़ोकस primarily on शोधन the theoretical समझना of सोशल प्रक्रियाओं.
Subject matter ranges from the micro स्तर of व्यक्तिगत agency और interaction to the मैक्रो स्तर of प्रणालियों और the सोशल structure.
The traditional focuses of समाजशास्त्र include सोशल stratification, सोशल class, culture, रेस और ethnicity, gender and कामुकता, सोशल गतिशीलता, धर्म, secularization, विधि, and deviance.
As सब spheres of इंसान activity हैं affected by the interplay between सोशल ढांचा and व्यक्तिगत agency, समाजशास्त्र रै gradually विस्तारित इसके फ़ोकस to further विषय, such as health, medical, सैन्य और penal institutions, the अंतरजाल, environmental sociology, political अर्थव्यवस्था और the भूमिका of सोशल कार्यकलाप in the विकास of वैज्ञानिक knowledge.
The range of सोशल scientific विधि रै also विस्तारित.
Social researchers draw upon a variety of qualitative and quantitative तकनीकों.
the भाषाई और सांस्कृतिक turns of the mid-twentieth सदी led to increasingly interpretative, hermeneutic, and philosophic approaches to the विश्लेषण of समाज.
conversely, recent decades have seen the वृद्धि of new analytically, mathematically and computationally rigorous तकनीकों, such as agent-based modelling and सोशल network विश्लेषण.
Sociology चाहिए नहीं be confused with various सामान्य social अध्ययन courses जिससे bear little relation to समाजशास्त्रीय सिद्धान्त or सोशल science research methodology.
Thunder is the sound caused by बिजली.
depending on the nature of the बिजली और अलहदा of the listener, थंडर can दायरा from a sharp, loud crack to a long, कम rumble ( brontide ).
the अचानक बढ़ाएँ in pressure और तापमान from lightning produces rapid विस्तार of the एयर surrounding और भीतर a bolt of lightning.
in turn, इस expansion of air creates a सोनिक शॉक वेव, समान to a sonic boom, जिससे produces the ध्वनि of thunder, प्रायः referred to as a clap, crack, or peal of thunder.
The distance of the lightning can be calculated by the श्रोता आधारित on the समय अंतराल इससे when the बिजली is seen to जब the ध्वनि is सुना.
पालमा (,, ), in पूरा पालमा de Mallorca, is the major नगर और port on the द्वीप of majorca ( mallorca ) and capital नगर of the autonomous जातियाँ of the balearic Islands in स्पेन.
The names ciutat de mallorca ( City of majorca ) and Ciutat ( नगर ) were used पहले the युद्ध of the स्पेनी उत्तराधिकार and हैं still used by लोगों in majorca.
however, the आधिकारिक name was Mallorca, the वही as the island.
it is situated on the south coast of the island on the खाड़ी of Palma.
as of the 2009 census, the population of the नगर of पालमा उचित was 401,270, and the जनसांख्यिकी of the संपूर्ण शहरी क्षेत्रफल थी 517,285, ranking as the बारहवीं largest शहरी क्षेत्रफल of स्पेन.
लगभग half of the total जनसांख्यिकी of Majorca live in पालमा.

Its विमानक्षेत्र, बेटे Sant Joan, serves over 22 million यात्री each साल.

Luthor is the archenemy of Superman, और as a high-status supervillain, रै भी come into विरोध with बैटमैन and other superheroes in the dc Universe.
निर्मित by जेरी Siegel और Joe shuster, the character पहला appeared in Action Comics # 23 ( अप्रैल 1940 ).
Luthor is वर्णित as `` a power-mad, evil scientist '' of ऊँची intelligence और incredible technological prowess.
luthor 's लक्ष्य typically center on killing सुपरमैन, the foremost बाधा to achieving the विलेन 's megalomaniacal लक्ष्य.
despite periodically wearing a powered बहि, luthor रै traditionally lacked superpowers or a डुअल identity.
the अक्षर थी originally चित्रित as a mad scientist जो, in the रग of pulp novels, wreaks havoc on the संसार साथ his अत्याधुनिक weaponry.
in उसके earliest appearances, Luthor is shown साथ a पूरा head of red बाल.

a 1960 स्टोरी by जेरी Siegel विस्तारित upon luthor 's origin और motivations, revealing उसे to be a childhood dost of सुपरमैन 's who खोया his बाल जब a आग नष्ट his प्रयोगशाला ; luthor vowed बदला.
Following the 1985 limited श्रेणी Crisis on अनन्त earths, the अक्षर was re-imagined as a machiavellian उद्योगपति and white-collar दण्ड, भी briefly सेवारत as President of the संयुक्त राज्य.

Martin लूथर किंग, Jr. Day is a संयुक्त राज्य federal holiday अंकन the जन्मदिवस of रेव. dr. मार्टिन लूथर King, Jr.
it is observed on the तीसरा Monday of January प्रत्येक साल, जिससे is around the समय of King 's जन्मदिवस, जनवरी 15.
The floating अवकाश is समान to छुट्टियाँ set under the वर्दी सोमवार अवकाश Act, हालांकि the अधिनियम predated the स्थापना of मार्टिन लूथर King, jr. दिन by 15 years.
किंग was the chief spokesman लिये nonviolent सक्रियता in the civil rights movement, which सफलतापूर्वक protested racial पक्षपात in संघीय और state विधि.
The campaign for a federal अवकाश in किंग 's honor began जल्द after his हत्या in 1968.
रोनाल्ड reagan हस्ताक्षरित the अवकाश into law in 1983, और it थी first observed on जनवरी 20, 1986.
At पहला, कुछ राज्य resisted observing the अवकाश as ऐसे, giving it वैकल्पिक names or combining it साथ other छुट्टियाँ.
it थी officially observed in all 50 राज्य for the first time in 2000.
the कैमरा phone solution allows तत्काल sharing of तस्वीरें.
As it 's स्वचालित और instant, the उपयोक्ता करता नहीं have to उपयोग a केबल or removable मीडिया to connect to a निजी कंप्यूटर.
a camera फोन is a मोबाईल फोन which is समर्थ to कैप्चर स्टिल छायाचित्र ( and प्रायः video ).
चूंकि जल्दी in the 21st सदी the majority of मोबाईल फोन in use हैं कैमरा phones.
सबसे कैमरा फोन are simpler than पृथक digital कैमरे.
Their usual फिक्स्ड फ़ोकस lenses and छोटी sensors limit उनके प्रदर्शन in ग़रीब lighting.
Lacking a शारीरिक शटर, सबसे have a long शटर lag.
फ्लैश, जहाँ present, is प्रायः कमजोर.
ऑप्टिकल zoom and तिपाई screws हैं rare.
कुछ also lack a USB connection, removable memory कार्ड, or other रास्ता of transferring their pictures अधिक जल्दी than by the फोन 's अंतर्निहित communication विशेषता.
कुछ of the more महंगी कैमरा फोन have तभी a few of these technical disadvantages, जिससे apply most acutely in low लाइट शर्तें और in कोई case have not inhibited उनके widespread use.
सबसे मॉडल लाइनों improve in these regards every year or two.
कुछ, ऐसे as the Droid Incredible तभी have a menu choice to start an application program to activate the कैमरा.
अन्य, such as the ब्लैकबेरी तूफ़ान 2, droid x, Motorola v980 और Nokia 5800 भी have a पृथक कैमरा बटन for quickness and convenience.
Windows फोन can be configured to operate as a कैमरा even if the फोन is asleep.
Some camera phones हैं designed to resemble पृथक low-end डिजिटल कॉम्पैक्ट cameras in appearance और to कुछ extent in features and picture quality, और हैं branded as both mobile phones and cameras, सहित निश्चित सोनी फोन.
the principal advantages of कैमरा फोन are लागत and compactness ; indeed लिये a user who carries a मोबाईल फोन anyway, the अतिरिक्त size और cost are negligible.
Smartphones that are camera phones may run mobile applications to add सामर्थ्य such as geotagging और चित्र stitching.
a few ऊँची end phones can उपयोग उनके touch screen to सीधा उनके camera to focus on a particular object in the फ़ील्ड of दृश्य, giving भी an अनुभवहीन उपयोक्ता a degree of फ़ोकस कंट्रोल exceeded तभी by seasoned फ़ोटोग्राफ़र using manual फ़ोकस.
`` whatever Happened to the man of Tomorrow ? '' is a 1986 comic book story featuring the DC Comics अक्षर of सुपरमैन.
Written by Alan Moore साथ help from long-time, and जल्द to be retiring, Superman एडिटर, जूलियस schwartz, the स्टोरी थी published in दो parts, beginning in सुपरमैन # 423 और समाप्ति in कार्रवाई Comics # 583, दोनो प्रकाशित in सितंबर 1986.
the स्टोरी was drawn by long-time कलाकार Curt Swan, in his फाइनल major योगदान to the सुपरमैन शीर्षक, and was inked by जार्ज pérez in the issue of सुपरमैन और कर्ट schaffenberger in the समस्या of कार्रवाई कॉमिक्स.
The स्टोरी was an imaginary टेल which told the final स्टोरी of the चांदी आयु सुपरमैन और उसके long history, जिससे थी being rebooted following the events of Crisis on अनन्त earths, before उसके आधुनिक introduction in the John Byrne series, the man of स्टील.
मूर चाही उसके प्लाट to honor the long history of the character और to serve as a पूरा conclusion to his mythology.
the स्टोरी is a frame story set ten years बाद Superman was last देखी, जहाँ लोइस Lane recounts the tale of the समाप्त of Superman 's career to a रिपोर्टर इससे the रोज़ ग्रह.

it is प्रयुक्त as an उदाहरण of how to बंद the long-time निरंतरता of a कॉमिक किताब character.

A short story is a brief work of literature, प्रायः लिखा in कथा गद्य.
उभरते इससे पहले मौखिक storytelling परंपराओं in the 17th century, the short story रै grown to encompass a देह of work so diverse as to defy easy characterization.
at इसके सबसे prototypical the छोटी स्टोरी सुविधाएँ a small cast of नामित वर्ण, और focuses on a self-contained incident साथ the intent of evoking a `` सिंगल प्रभाव '' or मनोदशा.
in so doing, छोटी कहानियां मेक उपयोग of प्लाट, अनुनाद, और अन्य डायनेमिक components to a far वृहद उपाधि than is typical of an किस्सा, yet to a दूर lesser degree than a अनोखा.
जबकि the short स्टोरी is largely distinct इससे the अनोखा, लेखक of both generally चित्रण इससे a आम pool of literary तकनीकों.
छोटी कहानियां have no set length.
in terms of शब्द count वहीँ is no आधिकारिक demarcation between an किस्सा, a छोटी story, and a novel.
बल्कि, the रूप 's parameters are दिए by the rhetorical और practical कॉन्टेक्स्ट in जिससे a given story is उत्पादित और माना, so कि कया constitutes a छोटी story may differ between genres, countries, eras, and commentators.
Like the अनोखा, the short story 's predominant आकार reflects the demands of the उपलब्धियाँ markets लिये publication, और the evolution of the रूप seems closely tied to the एवोल्यूशन of the publishing उद्योग और the सबमिशन दिशानिर्देश of its constituent घरों.
the छोटी story रै महरूम considered both an शिक्षुता रूप preceding अधिक lengthy works, and a crafted रूप in its अपना right, एकत्रित साथ in books of समान length, price, और वितरण as novels.
छोटी story लेखक may define उनके works as भाग of the artistic और निजी अभिव्यक्ति of the रूप.
वे may भी attempt to resist categorization by विधा and फिक्स्ड रूप.

the raccoon (, procyon lotor ), sometimes spelled racoon, भी ज्ञात as the common raccoon, उत्तर अमरीकी raccoon, उत्तरी raccoon and colloquially as कून, is a medium-sized स्तनधारी देशी to उत्तर अमेरिका.
The raccoon is the largest of the procyonid family, having a देह लंबाई of and a body वज़न of.
इसके grayish coat ज़्यादातर consists of dense underfur जिससे insulates विरूद्ध ठंडा weather.
Two of the raccoon 's सबसे distinctive features हैं इसके extremely dexterous सामने पंजे और its facial mask, जिससे are विषयवस्तु in the mythology of several देशी अमरीकी जनजातियों.
raccoons हैं विख्यात for उनके intelligence, with अध्ययन प्रर्दशित that they हैं समर्थ to याद the solution to कार्य लिये up to three सालो.
the diet of the omnivorous raccoon, which is प्रायः nocturnal, consists of about 40 % invertebrates, 33 % संयंत्र भोजन, and 27 % vertebrates.
The असली habitats of the raccoon are पतझड़ी and मिश्रित forests, लकिन due to उनके adaptability वे have विस्तारित उनके दायरा to mountainous areas, तटीय marshes, और urban क्षेत्रों, जहाँ कुछ homeowners consider them to be पीड़कों.
As a परिणाम of escapes और deliberate introductions in the mid-20th सदी, raccoons हैं अभी भी distributed आरपार the European मेनलैंड, the काकेशस region और Japan.
हालांकि previously विचार to be एकान्त, वहीँ is अभी evidence that raccoons engage in gender-specific सोशल behavior.
सम्बन्धित महिलाओं often share a आम area, जबकि unrelated males सजीव साथ in groups of up to चार पशु to maintain उनके स्थितियाँ विरूद्ध विदेशी males दौरान the mating ऋतु, and अन्य संभावित invaders.
घर range sizes vary anywhere इससे 3 हेक्टेयर ( 7 acres ) लिये महिलाओं in cities to 50 km2 ( 20 sq mi ) लिये males in prairies.
After a gestation काल of परिचय 65 दिनों, दो to पाँच यंग, ज्ञात as `` kits '', हैं born in spring.
The kits are subsequently उठाया by उनके माँ until dispersion in late fall.
हालांकि खिलाते raccoons have महरूम ज्ञात to सजीव over 20 years, उनके औसत जीवन प्रत्याशा in the जंगली is तभी 1.8 to 3.1 years.
in many क्षेत्रों, hunting और vehicular injury are the two सबसे आम causes of मौत.

The rapture is a पद in ईसाई eschatology जिससे refers to the `` being caught up '' discussed in 1 thessalonians 4:17, when the `` मुर्दे in मसीह '' और `` we जो are जिंदा और remain '' will be `` caught up in the clouds '' to meet `` the रब in the एयर ''.
The पद `` rapture '' is used in at तनिक दो होश.
In the pre-tribulation दृश्य, a group of people होगा be बाएँ behind on धरती बाद another समूह वस्तुतः पत्ते `` to मिलें the रब in the एयर. ''
इस is अभी the सबसे common use of the term, विशेषकर among fundamentalist Christians और in the संयुक्त States.
the other, older use of the पद `` rapture '' is बस as a synonym लिये the फाइनल क़यामत generally, without a विश्वास that a group of लोगों is बाएँ पीछे on धरती for an विस्तारित tribulation काल बाद the कार्यक्रम of 1 thessalonians 4:17.
इस भेद is important as some types of Christianity never refer to `` the rapture '' in धार्मिक शिक्षा, लकिन might उपयोग the older और more general sense of the शब्द `` rapture '' in referring to what happens दौरान the फाइनल resurrection.
There हैं many views among ईसाइयों regarding the समय of मसीह 's return ( सहित whether it होगा occur in एक event or two ), और various दृश्य regarding the destination of the aerial महफ़िल वर्णित in 1 Thessalonians 4.
Denominations such as रोमन catholics, Orthodox ईसाइयों, लूथरन Christians, और Reformed ईसाइयों believe in a rapture तभी in the भाव of a general final क़यामत, when मसीह returns a single time.
वे do not believe that a समूह of people is left behind on earth लिये an विस्तारित tribulation काल after the events of 1 thessalonians 4:17.
pre-tribulation rapture धर्मशास्त्र थी विकसित in the 1830s by जॉन Nelson Darby और the plymouth Brethren, और popularized in the संयुक्त राज्य in the early 20th सदी by the चौड़ी परिसंचरण of the scofield सन्दर्भ बाइबल.

The philistine शहरों of गाजा, ashdod, ashkelon, Ekron, and gath
The Philistines (,,, or ;, Plištim ), pleshet or peleset, यहूद a लोगों जो as part of the समुद्र peoples appeared in the दक्षिणी coastal क्षेत्रफल of canaan at the शुरूआत of the Iron आयु ( circa 1175 bc ), most संभवतः from the ईजियन region.
According to the Bible, वे शासित the five city-states ( the `` Philistine pentapolis '' ) of Gaza, ashkelon, Ashdod, ekron और gath, इससे Wadi गाजा in the दक्षिण to the Yarqon नदी in the north, लकिन साथ no फिक्स्ड border to the east.
The Bible paints उन्हें as the किंगडम of Israel 's most खतरनाक enemy.
Originating somewhere in the ईजियन, उनके population थी around 25,000 in the 12th सदी BC, उठती to a शिखर of 30,000 in the 11th सदी bc, of जिससे the Aegean तत्व थी नहीं अधिक than half the कुल, और perhaps much less.
nothing is ज्ञात for निश्चित परिचय the original भाषा or भाषाएं of the philistines, however वे यहूद नहीं भाग of the Semitic Canaanite population.
There is some सीमित प्रमाण in पक्ष of the assumption that the philistines यहूद indo-european-speakers either इससे यूनानियों and/or luwian अध्यक्षों इससे the coast of Asia नाबालिग.
Philistine-related शब्द मिला in the बाइबल हैं नहीं Semitic, and can in some cases, with reservations, be traced वापस to proto-indo-european जड़ें.
by the शुरूआत of the 1st Millennium bce they था अपनाया the सामान्य Canaanite भाषा of the region.
the हथियारबंद Services वोकेशनल Aptitude बैटरी ( asvab ) is a multiple choice परीक्षण, administered by the United States Military प्रवेश प्रसंस्करण कमांड, प्रयुक्त to determine qualification for enlistment in the United राज्य हथियारबंद forces.
it is often offered to अमरीकी ऊँची स्कूल students when वे are in the 10th, 11th and 12th grade, हालांकि anyone योग्य for enlistment may take it.
Although the test is administered by the military, it is not ( and never रै महरूम ) a आवश्यकता कि a test-taker साथ a qualifying स्कोर enlist in the हथियारबंद forces.
In वित्तीय हिसाब, a संतुलन चादर or statement of financial position is a सारांश of the financial balances of a sole बंदोबस्त, a कारोबार साझेदारी, a निगम or अन्य business organization, ऐसे as an LLC or an LLP.
एसेट, liabilities और स्वामित्व इक्विटी हैं listed as of a विशिष्ट date, such as the end of इसके financial साल.
A संतुलन sheet is often described as a `` snapshot of a company 's वित्तीय कंडीशन ''.
of the चार मौलिक वित्तीय statements, the संतुलन sheet is the only बयान जिससे applies to a सिंगल पाइंट in समय of a business ' पंचांग year.
a मानक कम्पनी balance sheet रै three parts : एसेट, liabilities and स्वामित्व इक्विटी.
the प्रमुख categories of assets हैं प्रायः listed पहला, और typically in अनुक्रम of चलनिधि.
Assets are followed by the liabilities.
the अंतर between the assets और the देनदारी is known as equity or the जाल assets or the जाल worth or पूंजी of the कम्पनी और according to the हिसाब equation, net worth जरूर बराबर assets ऋण देनदारी.
another रास्ता to dekh at the वही equation is कि एसेट equals देनदारी प्लस मालिक 's इक्विटी.
looking at the समीकरण in इस way shows how एसेट were financed : either by उधार money ( देयता ) or by using the owner 's धन ( मालिक 's इक्विटी ).
संतुलन चादरें are usually presented साथ एसेट in एक खण्ड और देनदारी और जाल worth in the अन्य खण्ड साथ the दो sections `` balancing. ''
A कारोबार operating entirely in cash can measure इसके profits by withdrawing the संपूर्ण bank balance at the समाप्त of the period, प्लस कोई नकदी in हाथ.
However, अनेक व्यवसायों हैं नहीं सशुल्क तत्काल ; they निर्माण up inventories of goods और वे acquire buildings and equipment.
in अन्य शब्द : व्यवसायों have एसेट and so they can not, भी if they want to, तत्काल turn ये into cash at the समाप्त of प्रत्येक काल.
प्रायः, ये व्यवसायों owe धन to आपूर्तिकर्ता and to कर अधिकारियों, and the proprietors do नहीं withdraw सब उनके original पूंजी and profits at the समाप्त of प्रत्येक काल.
In other शब्द businesses भी have liabilities.
.17 hornady मैग्नम rimfire, commonly known as the.17 HMR, is a rimfire राइफल कार्ट्रिज विकसित by the ammunition कम्पनी hornady in 2002.
it descended from the.22 मैग्नम by necking bas the.22 मैग्नम मामला to take a.17 कैलिबर ( 4.5 mm ) bullet, और it is more costly to shoot than परंपरागत.22 caliber rimfire cartridges.

The Schaumburg Flyers were a पेशेवर बेसबॉल team based in Schaumburg, Illinois, in the संयुक्त राज्य.

Rachel हन्ना वाइज़ ( / वाइस / ; born 7 March 1970 ) is an अंग्रेज़ी फिल्मी and थिएटर actress and former फ़ैशन मॉडल.
Weisz began उसके एक्टिंग करियर at ट्रिनिटी Hall, Cambridge in the जल्दी 1990s, तब started working in television, appearing in इंस्पेक्टर मोर्स, the अंग्रेजों mini-series स्कारलेट और Black, और the टेलीविज़न फिल्मी अधिवक्ताओं ii.
वो made उसके फिल्मी début in the film मौत Machine ( 1994 ), लकिन उसके भेदन भूमिका आए in the film Chain प्रतिक्रिया ( 1996 ), अग्रणी to a high-profile भूमिका as एवलिन Carnahan-O'Connell in the films The Mummy ( 1999 ) and the मम्मी Returns ( 2001 ).
अन्य notable films featuring Weisz हैं दुश्मन at the गेट्स, About a लड़के, constantine, the Fountain and The निरंतर माली, for which वो प्राप्त an Academy पुरस्कार, a Golden Globe और a स्क्रीन Actors ' गिल्ड पुरस्कार लिये her supporting role as Tessa quayle.
She रै महरूम labelled an `` अंग्रेज़ी rose '' चूंकि उसके नाबालिग role in चोरी Beauty ( 1996 ).
वाइज़ भी works in थिएटर.

वाइज़ 's performances भी include the 1999 Donmar Warehouse production of Tennessee Williams ' Suddenly, पिछला गर्मियाँ, और their 2009 पुनरुद्धार of A स्ट्रीटकार नामित ख्वाहिश.

वो रै recently निभाई Evanora in oz the Great और शक्तिशाली.
The अमरीकी सिविल War ( acw ), also ज्ञात as the युद्ध between the States or बस the Civil War ( देखिए naming ), was a सिविल युद्ध लड़ा इससे 1861 to 1865 between the संयुक्त राज्य ( the `` Union '' or the `` North '' ) and several Southern स्लेव राज्य कि घोषित their secession and formed the confederate राज्य of अमेरिका ( the `` confederacy '' or the `` South '' ).
the war था its उत्पत्ति in the समस्या of गुलामी, विशेषकर the एक्सटेंशन of slavery into the पश्चिमी territories.
विदेशी शक्तियां किया नहीं intervene.
बाद चार सालो of bloody combat that बाएँ over 600,000 सैनिको dead and नष्ट much of the दक्षिण 's अवसंरचना, the Confederacy collapsed, slavery was abolished, and the मुश्किल पुनर्निर्माण process of restoring नेशनल एकता और guaranteeing अधिकारों to the freed slaves began.
In the 1860 presidential election, republicans, led by Abraham Lincoln, opposed expanding slavery into संयुक्त राज्य ' territories.
lincoln won, लकिन before his inauguration on कूच 4, 1861, seven cotton-based स्लेव राज्य formed the Confederacy.
Outgoing Democratic अध्यक्ष जेम्स Buchanan और the आवक Republicans अस्वीकृत secession as illegal.
Lincoln 's inaugural पता declared उसके administration होता not initiate सिविल war.
Eight remaining slave राज्य continued to अस्वीकृत काल्स for secession.
Confederate शक्तियां जब्त numerous संघीय दुर्गों भीतर territory claimed by the confederacy.
A Peace सम्मेलन विफल to ढूँढें a compromise, और दोनो sides prepared लिये युद्ध.
The confederates assumed that European countries यहूद so निर्भर on `` King Cotton `` that वे होता intervene ; none did और none recognized the new confederate States of America.
Hostilities began on April 12, 1861, जब confederate शक्तियां fired upon Fort sumter, a कुंजी फोर्ट held by संघ सैनिकों in दक्षिण Carolina.
lincoln पुकारा for प्रत्येक state to provide troops to retake the fort ; नतीजतन, चार more स्लेव states joined the confederacy, bringing their कुल to ग्यारह.
the Union soon नियंत्रित the border states and स्थापित a naval blockade कि अबोध the दक्षिणी economy.
The Eastern थिएटर थी inconclusive in 1861–62.
the autumn 1862 Confederate अभियान into मेरीलैंड ( a Union राज्य ) ended with Confederate retreat at the बैटल of antietam, dissuading British हस्तक्षेप.
Lincoln issued the emancipation उदघोषणा, which made समाप्ति slavery a युद्ध लक्ष्य.
to the वेस्ट, by गर्मियाँ 1862 the Union नष्ट the Confederate river navy, तब much of उनके पश्चिमी सेना, और the Union at Vicksburg विभाजित the Confederacy in दो at the मिसिसिपी River.
in 1863, Robert E. Lee 's Confederate incursion उत्तर ended at the बैटल of gettysburg.
Western सफलताओं led to Ulysses S. ग्रान्ट command of सब संघ सेना in 1864.
in the पश्चिमी Theater, विलियम T. शरमन drove ईस्ट to capture अटलांटा और marched to the sea, destroying confederate अवसंरचना along the रास्ता.
the संघ marshaled the resources और जनशक्ति to attack the confederacy इससे all दिशानिर्देश, और could afford to लड़ो लड़ाइयों of अपघर्षण through the overland Campaign towards रिचमंड, the Confederate पूंजी.
the defending confederate army विफल, अग्रणी to Lee 's surrender to ग्रान्ट at Appomattox Court हाउस on अप्रैल 9, 1865.
the अमरीकी सिविल War थी एक of the earliest सच्चा औद्योगिक युद्धों.
railroads, the telegraph, steamships, और mass-produced हथियार यहूद employed extensively.
the mobilization of civilian factories, खानों, shipyards, banks, परिवहन and खाना आपूर्तियाँ सब foreshadowed संसार युद्ध i.
It remains the deadliest war in अमरीकी इतिहास, resulting in the deaths of an estimated 750,000 सैनिको and an undetermined number of civilian हताहत.
Historian जॉन huddleston estimates the death toll at ten percent of all उत्तरी males 20–45 सालो बूढ़ा, and 30 प्रतिशत of all दक्षिणी श्वेत males aged 18–40.
आलू ब्रैड is a रूप of ब्रैड in which आलू replaces a portion of the नियमित गेहूं आटा.
it is पकाया in a किस्में of methods, सहित by बेकिंग it on a hot तवे or pan, or in an oven.
It may be leavened or unleavened, और may have a किस्में of other संघटक baked into it.
the ratio of potato to wheat flour varies significantly from recipe to रेसिपी, with कुछ recipes having a बहुमत of आलू, और अन्य having a बहुमत of गेहूं आटा.
कुछ recipes call लिये mashed potatoes, साथ others calling for निर्जलित potato flakes.
it is available as a वाणिज्यिक product in अनेक countries, साथ समान विसंगतियाँ in संघटक, कुकिंग विधि, और अन्य variables.
The प्रशांत समय मण्डल observes मानक time by subtracting आठ घंटों इससे Coordinated सार्वभौमिक समय ( ).
The क्लॉक समय in इस मण्डल is आधारित on the औसत solar time of the 120th मध्याह्न west of the ग्रीनविच वेधशाला.
दौरान daylight छायांकन time, इसके समय ऑफसेट is.
In the United राज्य और कनाडा, this समय zone is generically called प्रशांत Time ( pt ).
Specifically, it is प्रशांत Standard Time ( PST ) when observing standard समय ( शीत ), and Pacific daylight समय ( पीडीटी ) जब observing daylight saving समय ( summer ).
सबसे of कनाडा uses daylight saving समय.
In मैक्सिको the UTC−8 समय zone is ज्ञात as the Northwest Zone, जिससे is synchronized साथ the u.S. पीडीटी daylight छायांकन अनुसूची.
the largest city in the Pacific समय मण्डल is लॉस एंजिल्स in कैलिफ़ोर्निया इससे यूएसए ; the नगर 's महानगर क्षेत्रफल is the largest in the मण्डल.
The मण्डल is एक घंटा ahead of the अलास्का समय मण्डल, एक घंटा behind the पहाड़ समय मण्डल और three घंटों पीछे the पूर्वी Time मण्डल.
स्टीरियो 8, commonly ज्ञात as the eight-track कार्ट्रिज, eight-track टेप, or simply eight-track, is a magnetic tape ध्वनि recording प्रौद्योगिकी.
it was लोकप्रिय in the संयुक्त राज्य from the mid-1960s through to the early 1980s, लकिन थी अपेक्षाकृत अनजान in many यूरोपीय countries.
it थी, however, बहुत लोकप्रिय in the संयुक्त Kingdom during इस काल.
Stereo 8 was created in 1964 by a consortium led by विधेयक lear of Lear Jet निगम, साथ साथ ampex, घाट मोटर कम्पनी, General मोटर्स, Motorola, and आरसीए विक्टर Records ( आरसीए ).
it थी a further विकास of the similar stereo-pak four-track कार्ट्रिज निर्मित by अर्ल `` Madman '' Muntz.
a later quadraphonic संस्करण of the स्वरूप थी घोषित by RCA in April 1970 and first known as Quad-8, तब later बदला to बस q8.
Ramesses ii ( 1303 BC – जुलाई or अगस्त 1213 BC ; Egyptian :, alternatively transcribed as Rameses और Ramses or ), referred to as रामेसेस the Great, थी the third Egyptian pharaoh ( reigned 1279 bc – 1213 bc ) of the उन्नीसवीं dynasty.
he is often regarded as the महानतम, सबसे celebrated, और सबसे powerful pharaoh of the मिश्र Empire.
उसके successors और बाद उन्होंने called उसे the `` Great Ancestor. ''
रामेसेस II led अनेक सैन्य रिझाने into the levant, re-asserting मिश्र control over Canaan.
He भी led expeditions to the south, into नुबिया, commemorated in inscriptions at beit el-wali और Gerf Hussein.
At age चौदह, Ramesses थी नियुक्त प्रिंस रीजेंट by his father सेती i.
he is believed to have taken the सिंहासन in his लेट किशोर और is known to have शासित मिश्र इससे 1279 bc to 1213 bc for 66 सालो and 2 महीने, according to both manetho और मिश्र 's समकालीन ऐतिहासिक records.
He was एकबार कहा to have lived to be 99 सालो old, लकिन it is more संभावित कि he died in उसके 90th or 91st साल.
If he became Pharaoh in 1279 BC as सबसे egyptologists today believe, he होता have assumed the सिंहासन on may 31, 1279 bc, आधारित on उसके ज्ञात accession date of III Shemu दिन 27.
Ramesses ii celebrated an unprecedented 14 sed त्यौहार ( the पहला आयोजित बाद तीस सालो of a pharaoh 's शासनकाल, और तब प्रत्येक तीन सालो ) during उसके reign—more than any अन्य pharaoh.
on उसके death, he थी buried in a मकबरा in the घाटी of the किंग्स ; उसके body थी later स्थानांतरित to a royal संचय जहाँ it थी discovered in 1881, और is now on display in the कायरो संग्रहालय.
the early भाग of उसके शासनकाल थी focused on भवन cities, मंदिरों and स्मारक.
he established the city of pi-ramesses in the nile डेल्टा as his new पूंजी and main आधार for his अभियान in Syria.
This नगर was built on the remains of the city of avaris, the पूंजी of the Hyksos जब वे took over, और थी the location of the प्रमुख टेम्पल of नियत.
he is also ज्ञात as ozymandias in the यूनानी sources, इससे a लिप्यन्तरण into यूनानी of a भाग of रामेसेस 's throne नाम,, `` Ra 's mighty सच्चाई, chosen of ra ''.
The टेक्सास रेंजरों are a professional बेसबॉल team स्तिथ in the Dallas-Fort Worth Metroplex, आधारित in Arlington, Texas.
The Rangers मताधिकार is फिलहाल a सदस्य of the पश्चिमी Division of प्रमुख लीग Baseball 's अमरीकी लीग.
चूंकि, the Rangers have played in रेंजरों Ballpark in Arlington in आर्लिंगटन, Texas.
The टोली 's name is उधार इससे the प्रसिद्ध विधि enforcement agency of the वही नाम.
The franchise was स्थापित in 1961 by the name of the वॉशिंगटन सीनेटरों, an विस्तार टोली awarded to Washington, d.C., बाद the नगर 's first ballclub, the असली वॉशिंगटन Senators, moved to Minnesota और became the जुड़वा.
After the ऋतु, the new सीनेटरों स्थानांतरित to आर्लिंगटन, टेक्सास, और debuted as the रेंजरों the following वसन्त.
the टेक्सास Rangers बेसबॉल Club रै बना छह appearances in the एमएलबी postseason, सब following प्रभाग championships, in 1996, 1998, 1999, 2010, 2011 and 2012.
in 2010, the Rangers advanced पास्ट the प्रभाग Series लिये the पहला time, defeating the tampa Bay किरणें.
टेक्सास तब brought home उनके पहला American League Pennant बाद beating the New York Yankees in छह खेल.
in the 2010 World श्रेणी, the मताधिकार 's पहला, the Rangers गिरी to the San फ्रांसिस्को दिग्गज in five games.
Their लोन विजय बना उन्हें the पहला टेक्सास team to win a World Series game, the Houston एस्टर्स having महरूम swept in उनके 2005 संसार श्रेणी appearance.
वे दोहराया as अमरीकी लीग champions the following year, then खोया the 2011 संसार श्रेणी to the st. लुई कार्डिनल्स in सात खेल.
gaius जूलियस Caesar (, जुलाई 100 bc – 15 March 44 bc ) थी a रोमन सामान्य, statesman, कौंसुल and notable लेखक of Latin गद्य.
He निभाई a नाजुक भूमिका in the कार्यक्रम कि led to the निधन of the रोमन Republic और the rise of the रोमन साम्राज्य.
In 60 BC, सीज़र, Crassus और Pompey formed a राजनैतिक गठबंधन that थी to dominate रोमन राजनीती for अनेक सालो.
Their attempts to amass power through populist tactics यहूद opposed by the conservative elite भीतर the रोमन Senate, among उन्हें केटो the Younger साथ the बारंबार support of सिसरो.
Caesar 's conquest of Gaul, समाप्त by 51 BC, विस्तारित रोम 's territory to the अंग्रेज़ी Channel and the राइन.
सीज़र became the पहला रोमन general to क्रॉस both जब he built a bridge आरपार the राइन और conducted the first invasion of ब्रिटेन.
ये achievements granted उसे बेमेल सैन्य power और threatened to eclipse the standing of pompey, who था realigned himself with the सीनेट after the मौत of crassus in 53 bc.
साथ the Gallic युद्धों concluded, the Senate ordered सीज़र to lay down उसके सैन्य कमांड and वापसी to रोम.
सीज़र refused, और चिह्नित उसके defiance in 49 BC by क्रासिंग the rubicon साथ a लीजन, leaving his province and illegally प्रवेश रोमन territory अंतर्गत arms.
सिविल युद्ध resulted, इससे which he उभरा as the unrivaled नेता of Rome.
बाद assuming कंट्रोल of सरकारी, सीज़र began a program of सोशल और governmental reforms, सहित the सृष्टि of the Julian पंचांग.
He centralised the अफसरशाही of the Republic और was आखिरकार proclaimed `` तानाशाह in perpetuity ''.
लकिन the underlying राजनैतिक विरोध had not महरूम resolved, और on the ides of कूच ( 15 कूच ) 44 bc, सीज़र थी assassinated by a group of सीनेटरों led by मार्कस junius ब्रूटस.
a नई श्रेणी of civil युद्धों broke आउट, and the संवैधानिक government of the Republic was never लौटी.
सीज़र 's adopted वारिस octavian, later ज्ञात as Augustus, रोज़ to एकमात्र power, and the era of the Roman साम्राज्य began.
much of सीज़र 's जीवन is known इससे उसके own accounts of उसके सैन्य campaigns, and from अन्य समकालीन sources, मुख्यतः the अक्षर और speeches of सिसरो और the historical कृतियाँ of Sallust.
the later biographies of सीज़र by Suetonius और Plutarch are also प्रमुख स्त्रोत.
सीज़र is deemed to be one of the महानतम military कमांडरों of इतिहास.

The आधिकारिक भाषा of सीरियल, English, the former colonial भाषा, थी chosen to facilitate the सांस्कृतिक and भाषाई unity of the देश.
अंग्रेज़ी, however, remains an विशेष बचाना of the देश 's urban elite, and is not widely spoken in rural areas, जिससे comprise तीन quarters of the देशों population.

in the संयुक्त राज्य, the title of federal न्यायधीश usually means a न्यायधीश नियुक्त by the अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य और confirmed by the United States Senate pursuant to the नियुक्ति clause in आलेख ii of the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान.
in जोड to the Supreme अदालत of the United राज्य, whose existence और कुछ पहलुओं of जिनकी क्षेत्राधिकार are beyond the संवैधानिक power of कॉंग्रेस to alter, अधिनियमों of Congress have established 13 न्यायालयों of appeals ( भी पुकारा `` सर्किट courts '' ) with appellate क्षेत्राधिकार over different regions of the United राज्य, और 94 संयुक्त राज्य ज़िला न्यायालयों.
Every न्यायधीश नियुक्त to such a अदालत may be categorized as a संघीय न्यायधीश ; such positions शामिल the मुख्य इंसाफ and संबद्ध Justices of the Supreme अदालत, सर्किट न्यायाधीशों of the न्यायालयों of appeals, and ज़िला judges of the United States ज़िला न्यायालयों.
All of ये न्यायाधीशों described thus दूर हैं referred to sometimes as `` आलेख III न्यायाधीशों '' क्युकी वे कसरत the न्यायिक शक्ति vested in the judicial शाखा of the federal government by आलेख III of the u.S. संविधान.
In जोड, न्यायाधीशों of the Court of International Trade कसरत judicial शक्ति pursuant to आलेख iii.
Other न्यायाधीशों serving in the संघीय न्यायालयों, सहित मजिस्ट्रेट न्यायाधीशों और bankruptcy न्यायाधीशों, हैं भी sometimes referred to as `` संघीय न्यायाधीशों '' ; however, वे हैं neither appointed by the अध्यक्ष nor confirmed by the Senate, और उनके शक्ति गर्भाशयी from Article I बजाय.
See Article I और आलेख iii अधिकरणों.

Furtado 's कार्य रै earned उसके numerous awards और accolades, सहित 2 Grammy पुरस्कार, 10 Juno Awards, 3 MuchMusic Video Awards and a स्टार on Canada 's Walk of कीर्ति.

the somatosensory प्रणाली is a विविध sensory प्रणाली comprising the receptors और प्रसंस्करण केंद्रों to उपज the संवेदी modalities such as touch, temperature, proprioception ( body स्थिति ), and nociception ( पीड़ा ).
The संवेदी receptors cover the स्किन and epithelia, skeletal मांसपेशियां, हड्डियों और joints, आतंरिक organs, और the cardiovascular प्रणाली.
जबकि टच is considered एक of the पाँच traditional होश, the impression of टच is formed from several modalities.
In medicine, the colloquial पद `` टच '' is प्रायः replaced साथ `` दैहिक senses '' to better प्रतिबिंबित the variety of mechanisms शामिल.
Somatic senses हैं sometimes referred to as somesthetic होश, साथ the understanding कि somesthesis शामिल touch, proprioception और ( depending on usage ) also haptic बोध.
The प्रणाली reacts to diverse stimuli using अलग receptors : thermoreceptors, nociceptors, mechanoreceptors और chemoreceptors.
हस्तांतरण of सूचना इससे the receptors गुजरता via sensory nerves through tracts in the spinal cord and into the brain.
Processing primarily occurs in the primary somatosensory क्षेत्रफल in the parietal पालि of the cerebral cortex.
the cortical homunculus थी devised by वाइल्डर Penfield.
At इसके सरलतम, the प्रणाली works जब कार्यकलाप in a संवेदी न्यूरॉन is triggered by a specific stimulus ऐसे as ऊष्मा ; इस सिग्नल आखिरकार passes to an क्षेत्रफल in the brain uniquely attributed to that क्षेत्रफल on the body—this allows the processed stimulus to be felt at the correct location.
The point-to-point mapping of the देह surfaces in the brain is called a homunculus and is essential in the सृष्टि of a देह चित्र.
This brain-surface ( `` cortical '' ) map is not अपरिवर्तनीय, however.
नाटकीय शिफ्ट can occur in response to स्ट्रोक or injury.
magnolia is a विशाल genus of परिचय 210 flowering plant प्रजाति in the subfamily magnolioideae of the परिवार magnoliaceae.
it is नामित बाद फ्रेंच botanist पियरे magnol.
Magnolia is an प्राचीन genus.
Appearing before मधुमक्खियों did, the पुष्प evolved to प्रोत्साहित परागण by beetles.
To avoid damage इससे pollinating भृंग, the carpels of magnolia flowers are अत्यधिक मुश्किल.
fossilised नमूनों of Magnolia acuminata have महरूम found डेटिंग to 20 million सालो ago, और of पौधे identifiably belonging to the Magnoliaceae डेटिंग to 95 million सालो ago.
Another aspect of magnolias that is considered to represent an ancestral state is कि the पुष्प कली is enclosed in a bract बल्कि than in sepals ; the perianth parts are undifferentiated and पुकारा tepals बल्कि than distinct sepals and पंखुड़ियों.
Magnolia साझा the tepal characteristic साथ अनेक other flowering पौधे near the आधार of the flowering plant lineage ऐसे as amborella और nymphaea ( as खूब as साथ अनेक more recently derived plants such as लिलि ).
The प्राकृतिक range of Magnolia प्रजाति is a disjunct वितरण, साथ a main centre in east और southeast एशिया और a secondary केन्द्र in पूर्वी उत्तर America, सेंट्रल अमेरिका, the वेस्ट इंडीज, and कुछ species in दक्षिण America.

cross-country स्कीइंग ( or xc स्कीइंग ) is a रूप of स्की touring in जिससे participants propel themselves across snow-covered मैदान using skis and डंडे.

a use tax in संयुक्त राज्य is complementary to बिक्री कर जिससे अर्थात्, if you ख़रीदे a taxable product/services बगैर paying कोई बिक्री कर to vendor, you owe use कर.
तुम जरूर स्वः assess use tax and pay it सीधे to the state जहाँ the products यहूद consumed or services यहूद rendered.
Use कर typically is a कर on खपत लकिन if तुम buy an item ( बगैर paying बिक्री tax ) and store it in your गोदाम initially, उपयोग tax applies to कि स्थान जहाँ goods were stored.
Later on जब the final खपत takes place at some अन्य स्थान, you हैं जरूरी to अदा the अवकल of कर रेट to the jurisdiction of परम प्लेस of consumption.
इस वाकई अर्थात् कि तुम do n't have to pay दोनो Sales कर as well as उपयोग Tax on एक transaction.
it is only एक or the अन्य कि तुम हैं जरूरी to अदा on खरीदें of taxable products/services.
if विक्रेता करता n't चार्ज कोई बिक्री tax on इसके चालान then it is the दायित्व of the buyer to स्वः assess उपयोग tax और अदा it to the उचित jurisdication.
उपयोग कर is generally चार्ज at the same कर rate of बिक्री कर but in कुछ states the tax rate is अलग.
उपयोग tax is भी termed as `` Consumption कर '' or `` Consumer उपयोग कर ''.
a उपयोग tax is a प्रकार of excise कर levied in the United राज्य by numerous राज्य governments.
it is assessed upon ठोस निजी प्रॉपर्टी खरीदा by a resident of the assessing राज्य for उपयोग, भंडार, or consumption in कि राज्य ( not लिये पुनर्विक्रय ), regardless of जहाँ the खरीदें took place.
if a resident of a राज्य makes a purchase within his home राज्य, पूरा sales tax is paid at the time of the transaction.
The उपयोग कर applies जब a निवासी of the assessing state purchases an item कि is नहीं विषय to his घर राज्य 's बिक्री कर.
प्रायः, इस is due to out-of-state purchases, as well as ordering items through the मेल, by फोन, or over the अंतरजाल इससे अन्य states.
the उपयोग tax is typically assessed at the वही रेट as the sales tax that would have महरूम owed ( if कोई ) था the वही goods महरूम खरीदा in the राज्य of residence.
For उदाहरण, a resident of Massachusetts, with a 6.25 % `` बिक्री and उपयोग tax '' on निश्चित goods और services, purchases non-exempt goods or सेवाएं in नई हैम्पशायर लिये उपयोग, भंडार or अन्य consumption in मैसाचुसेट्स.
अंतर्गत नई Hampshire विधि, the नई Hampshire विक्रेता collects no बिक्री taxes on the goods, but the मैसाचुसेट्स purchaser/user जरूर still अदा 6.25 % of the sales price directly to the Department of आय in मैसाचुसेट्स as a use tax.
if the same goods हैं purchased in a us राज्य कि करता collect बिक्री कर for ऐसे goods at समय of खरीदें, whatever कर यहूद सशुल्क by the purchaser to कि राज्य can be deducted ( as a कर क्रेडिट ) from the 6.25 % owed for subsequent use, storage or consumption in Massachusetts.
With few exceptions, no राज्य 's vendors will चार्ज the native राज्य 's sales कर on goods shipped आउट of राज्य, अर्थ सब goods ordered इससे out-of-state हैं essentially फ़्री of बिक्री कर.
The purchaser is इसलिए जरूरी to declare and अदा the उपयोग tax to उसके home राज्य on ये ordered goods.
The assessing क्षेत्राधिकार may मेक the use कर देय annually, but some राज्य require a मासिक भुगतान.
लिये उदाहरण, जहाँ a Vermont निवासी has not paid at तनिक 6 % sales tax on property brought in लिये use in the राज्य, वर्मांट विधि requires दाखिल a कर वापसी ( Form su-452 और payment ) by the 20th दिन of the month following non-exempt purchases to avoid a $ 50 लेट शुल्क, a 5 % दंड प्रति माह, to a अधिकतम of 25 %, plus statutory ब्याज on the unpaid कर and penalties.
ठेठ छूटों शामिल purchases by charitable non-profit संगठन or सरकारी agencies, purchases लिये resale in commerce, and purchases via `` casual बिक्री '' by individuals नहीं in the ordinary course of कारोबार.
भी note that वहीँ are thousands of कर jurisdictions in the u.S. and many have ever-changing lists of specific types of goods और services that are नहीं taxable.
as an illustration of the complexities : a 2006 मैसाचुसेट्स law requires payment of कर on `` pre-written '' ( not कस्टम ) तन्त्र खरीदा और डाउनलोड over the Internet for installation और उपयोग in मैसाचुसेट्स, regardless of जहाँ it originates.
However, the actual use of the वही तन्त्र downloaded by a Massachusetts निवासी to a सर्वर in another राज्य remains a non-taxed `` सेवा ''.
In कंट्रास्ट, अरकंसास generally does not tax anything delivered over the अंतरजाल ( such as downloaded तन्त्र or म्यूज़िक ), except VoIP which is specifically defined as taxable `` दूरसंचार सेवाएं ''.
तन्त्र ( pre-written or custom ) `` delivered thru a tangible मीडियम '' ( i.e., on disk ) in अरकंसास is taxable भी if ordered online, except `` कस्टम तन्त्र लिये a particular ग्राहक '' which is non-taxable `` प्रोग्रामिंग services '' even if delivered on a डिस्क.
in सबसे cases, this complexity is भाग of the underlying बिक्री tax laws ; लकिन जबकि a brick-and-mortar स्टोर has to सौदे साथ तभी the sales कर कानून of इसके अपना location, remote sellers have to सौदे with the use कर laws of अनेक jurisdictions—up to प्रत्येक us राज्य and locality that प्रकृती them, if the company रै a presence or `` nexus '' in प्रत्येक राज्य ( as विशाल `` brick-and-mortar '' विक्रेता जैसे wal-mart और बेहतरीन ख़रीदे do ).
in आयुर्विज्ञान, pulmonary hypertension ( ph ) is an बढ़ाएँ of blood दबाव in the pulmonary धमनी, pulmonary रग, or pulmonary capillaries, साथ ज्ञात as the lung vasculature, leading to shortness of साँस, dizziness, fainting, and other symptoms, सब of जिससे are exacerbated by exertion.
pulmonary hypertension can be a कठोर बीमारी with a markedly decreased exercise सहिष्णुता and दिल विफलता.
it थी पहला identified by Dr. अर्नस्ट वोन romberg in 1891.
According to the सबसे recent classification, it can be एक of पाँच अलग प्रकार : arterial, venous, hypoxic, thromboembolic or विविध.

in computer विज्ञान, सरणी प्रोग्रामिंग भाषाएं ( भी known as vector or multidimensional भाषाएं ) generalize परिचालन on scalars to लागू transparently to सदिश, matrices, और higher dimensional arrays.
Array प्रोग्रामिंग primitives concisely एक्स्प्रेस broad विचार about आंकड़ा हेरफेर.
the level of conciseness can be dramatic in certain cases : it is नहीं uncommon to find array प्रोग्रामिंग language one-liners that require more than a युगल of pages of जावा कोड.
APL, designed by केन Iverson, थी the पहला प्रोग्रामिंग language to provide array प्रोग्रामिंग सामर्थ्य.
The mnemonic APL refers to the title of his seminal book `` A Programming भाषा '' और not to arrays प्रति se. Iverson 's contribution to rigor और स्पष्टता was संभवतः more महत्वपूर्ण than the simple एक्सटेंशन of dimensions to कृत्यों.
in the संयुक्त राज्य an annuity contract is निर्मित when an insured party, प्रायः an individual, pays a life बीमे company a सिंगल प्रीमियम कि होगा बाद be distributed वापस to the insured party over समय.
Annuity अनुबंध traditionally provide a guaranteed distribution of आय over समय, such as via फिक्स्ड भुगतान, until the death of the व्यक्ति or व्यक्तियों named in the contract or until a फाइनल तिथि, whichever आता first.
However, the बहुमत of आधुनिक annuity ग्राहक use annuities only to accumulate funds free of income और पूंजी gains taxes and to बाद लो lump-sum withdrawals without using the guaranteed-income-for-life विशेषता.
अध्यक्ष Barack ओबामा.

एजेंसी debt भी known as an एजेंसी बंध is a सुरक्षा, प्रायः a बंध, issued by a U.S. government-sponsored एजेंसी.
The offerings of ये एजेंसियों हैं समर्थित लकिन not guaranteed by the us सरकारी चूंकि the agencies हैं निजी entities.
Some prominent issuers of these प्रतिभूति हैं Student ऋण Marketing Association ( sallie mae ), Federal National Mortgage Association ( Fannie Mae ) और संघीय Home Loan बंधक Corporation ( फ्रेडी मैक ).

Three nuclear-powered American warships, ( शीर्ष to bottom ) nuclear cruisers uss Bainbridge and USS long बीच with uss एंटरप्राइज़ the पहला nuclear-powered aircraft वाहक in 1964.

Nuclear शक्ति is the उपयोग of sustained nuclear परिवर्द्धन to generate heat and विद्युत.
नाभिकीय शक्ति पौधे provided परिचय 5.7 % of the संसार 's उर्जा and 13 % of the world 's electricity, in 2012.
in 2013, the iaea report कि there are 437 operational nuclear शक्ति रिएक्टरों ( हालांकि not all हैं producing विद्युत ), in 31 देशों.
in addition, there हैं approximately 140 नवल vessels using नाभिकीय नोदन in आपरेशन, powered by कुछ 180 रिएक्टरों.
वहीँ is an जारी बहस परिचय the use of नाभिकीय energy.
Proponents, ऐसे as the संसार नाभिकीय संघ, the IAEA and पर्यावरणविद for नाभिकीय उर्जा contend कि nuclear power is a sustainable उर्जा सोर्स that reduces carbon emissions.
Opponents, such as ग्रीनपीस अंतरराष्ट्रीय और nirs, believe कि नाभिकीय power मुद्राएँ अनेक खतरे to लोगों और the environment.
Nuclear शक्ति plant दुर्घटनाओं शामिल the chernobyl विपत्ति ( 1986 ), फुकुशिमा daiichi nuclear विपत्ति ( 2011 ), और the तीन मील द्वीप दुर्घटना ( 1979 ).
There have भी महरूम कुछ nuclear-powered पनडुब्बी mishaps.
शोध into सुरक्षा improvements is continuing और नाभिकीय संलयन, believed to be safer, may be used in the भविष्य.
as of 2012, according to the iaea, विश्वव्यापी वहीँ were 68 सिविल नाभिकीय power रिएक्टरों under निर्माण in 15 countries.
in the US the पंक्तियां of लगभग half its रिएक्टरों have महरूम विस्तारित to 60 सालो, और योजनाएँ to build another dozen हैं अंतर्गत serious विचार.
However, Japan 's 2011 Fukushima Daiichi nuclear विपत्ति prompted a पुनर्विचार of nuclear energy नीति in अनेक countries.
Germany decided to close सब इसके रिएक्टरों by 2022, and इटली रै banned नाभिकीय शक्ति.
Following फुकुशिमा, the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Energy एजेंसी halved इसके estimate of अतिरिक्त नाभिकीय generating capacity to be built by 2035.
Photograph of the Berlin वॉल taken इससे the वेस्ट पक्ष.
The वॉल was built in 1961 to prevent ईस्ट germans इससे fleeing इससे साम्यवादी.
it थी an iconic प्रतीक of the Cold War और its fall in 1989 marked the end of the युद्ध.
the ठंडा युद्ध, प्रायः dated इससे 1947 to 1991, थी a sustained state of राजनैतिक और सैन्य टेंशन between powers in the पश्चिमी bloc, वर्चस्व by the संयुक्त राज्य with नाटो among its allies, और शक्तियां in the पूर्वी bloc, वर्चस्व by the सोवियत Union along साथ the वॉरसॉ अनुबंध.
इस began after the कामयाबी of their temporary wartime alliance विरूद्ध नाजी जर्मनी, leaving the USSR और the us as दो superpowers साथ profound economic और political differences.
a न्यूट्रल faction arose साथ the Non-Aligned Movement founded by मिश्र, इण्डिया, और यूगोस्लाविया ; this गुट अस्वीकृत संघ साथ either the US-led West or the soviet-led ईस्ट.
The ठंडा युद्ध was so नामित क्युकी the two major powers—each possessing नाभिकीय हथियार और thereby threatened साथ mutual assured destruction —never मिले in सीधा सैन्य कॉम्बैट.
Instead, in their संघर्ष for global influence वे engaged in जारी मनोवैज्ञानिक warfare और in नियमित indirect confrontations through प्रॉक्सी युद्धों.
Cycles of सापेक्ष शांत होता be followed by high टेंशन, which could have led to world युद्ध.
the tensest times were दौरान the बर्लिन नाकेबंदी ( 1948–1949 ), the Korean War ( 1950–1953 ), the Suez संकट ( 1956 ), the बर्लिन संकट of 1961, the Cuban missile संकट ( 1962 ), the वियतनाम युद्ध ( 1959–1975 ), the Yom kippur युद्ध ( 1973 ), the सोवियत war in Afghanistan ( 1979–1989 ), the सोवियत downing of Korean एयर लाइनों उड़ान 007 ( 1983 ), and the `` Able Archer '' नाटो military exercises ( 1983 ).
the conflict was expressed through military coalitions, strategic conventional फ़ोर्स deployments, extensive सहायता to क्लाएंट राज्य, espionage, massive propaganda campaigns, conventional और nuclear arms races, appeals to neutral राष्ट्र, rivalry at खेल कार्यक्रम ( in particular the ओलंपिक ), and technological प्रतियोगिताओं such as the स्पेस रेस.
the us and USSR became शामिल in political और सैन्य विरोध in the तीसरा World countries of लैटिन अमेरिका, अफ़्रीकी, the Middle East, and southeast एशिया.
To alleviate the risk of a संभावित nuclear war, दोनो पहलू sought राहत of राजनैतिक तनाव through détente in the 1970s.
in the 1980s, the संयुक्त States increased diplomatic, सैन्य, and economic pressures on the सोवियत संघ, at a समय when the कम्युनिस्ट राज्य was already suffering इससे economic stagnation.
In the mid-1980s, the नई Soviet अध्यक्ष मिखाइल Gorbachev introduced the liberalizing reforms of perestroika ( `` reorganization '', 1987 ) and ग्लास्नोस्त ( `` खुलेपन '', ca. 1985 ).
pressures लिये नेशनल स्वतंत्रता grew stronger in Eastern यूरोपीय, विशेषकर Poland.
वे reached a तोड़कर पाइंट when गोर्बाचेव refused to उपयोग सोवियत सैनिकों to support the faltering सरकारी of ईस्ट Germany in late 1989.
Within weeks all the उपग्रह राज्य broke free from Moscow in a शांतिपूर्ण wave of revolutions ( वहीँ थी some हिंसा in रोमानिया ).
The pressures escalated inside the Soviet Union, where साम्यवादी fell और the ussr थी formally dissolved in late 1991.
the United राज्य remained as the world 's तभी महाशक्ति.
The Cold युद्ध और its events have left a significant legacy, और it is often referred to in popular संस्कृति, विशेषकर in media featuring विषयवस्तु of espionage and the threat of nuclear warfare.
pikes Peak राज्य Park is a राज्य park of आयोवा, यूएसए, featuring a bluff overlooking the अपर मिसिसिपी River opposite the संगम of the Wisconsin नदी.
the पार्क is संचालित by the आयोवा विभाग of प्राकृतिक संसाधन.
It is nearly a हजार एकड़ ( 4 km2 ) in extent.
The निकटतम नगर is मैकग्रेगर, आयोवा.
आयोवा राजमार्ग 76 लगभग defines इसके उत्तरी boundary.
it gets इसके name इससे the आयोवा incarnation of pikes शिखर, a particularly ऊँची पाइंट निहार the gorge of the अपर मिसिसिपी, और जैसे pikes शिखर in Colorado, is नामित for Zebulon पाइक.
वहीँ are चढ़ाई trails, campgrounds और rv सुविधाएं.
पहाड़ बाइक हैं permitted in निश्चित portions of the पार्क.
Aside इससे recreational विकास, the जमीन in the पार्क was never साफ and to a विशाल extent remains as it थी पहले the आगमन of श्वेत settlement.
It is भाग of a larger complex of पार्क, reserves and refuges जिससे शामिल पुतला Mounds National स्मारक, the विभिन्न components of the Yellow नदी State वन, the विशाल Upper मिसिसिपी नदी National वन्यजीव and मछली शरण and much छोटी, much less well ज्ञात driftless क्षेत्रफल नेशनल वन्यजीव शरण.

बात रेडियो is a रेडियो format containing discussion परिचय topical issues.
Most shows हैं regularly hosted by a single व्यक्तिगत, और often feature साक्षात्कार साथ a क्रमांक of different guests.
बात रेडियो typically शामिल an तत्व of listener भागीदारी, प्रायः by broadcasting सजीव conversations between the मेजबान और listeners जो `` कॉल in '' ( usually via टेलीफोन ) to the दिखाएँ.
श्रोता contributions हैं usually screened by a show 's निर्माता ( s ) in अनुक्रम to अधिकतम audience ब्याज और, in the case of वाणिज्यिक talk रेडियो, आकर्षित विज्ञापनदाता.
generally, the shows हैं organized into खण्ड, each separated by a ठहराना लिये advertisements ; however, in पब्लिक or non-commercial radio, music is sometimes played in place of commercials to पृथक the कार्यक्रम segments.
विसंगतियाँ of बात रेडियो include conservative बात, hot बात, liberal talk and sports बात.
जबकि बात रेडियो has historically been associated साथ AM/FM, starting around 2005 the प्रौद्योगिकी लिये Internet-based talk-radio shows became लागत प्रभावी in the रूप of podcasts.
अभी, it is संभावित लिये an individual to उपयोग a variety of services to मेजबान an internet-based talk-radio show without carriage by a traditional रेडियो स्टेशन.
In जोड tv programming इससे talk और news आउटलेट ऐसे as बीबीसी, CNN, Bloomberg and फॉक्स हैं now often उपलब्धियाँ expanding the संसार of talk रेडियो further.
बात रेडियो सुनना is अभी enjoyed not only on radios, लकिन a चौड़ी किस्में of other devices and सेवाएं including PCs using iTunes, station निर्देशिका ऐसे as Tunein, दिखाएँ निर्देशिका smartphones साथ apps such as stitcher.
Hippa is a genus of decapod crustaceans in the family hippidae, containing the following species:
hippa adactyla Fabricius, 1787
hippa admirabilis ( Thallwitz, 1892 )
hippa alcimede ( de Man, 1902 )
hippa australis Hale, 1927
hippa carcineutes holthuis & Manning, 1970
hippa celaeno ( de man, 1896 )
Hippa granulatus ( borradaile, 1904 )
Hippa hirtipes ( दाना, 1852 )
hippa indica haig, Murugan & बालकृष्णन Nair, 1986
Hippa marmorata ( hombron & jacquinot, 1846 )
hippa ovalis ( A. milne-edwards, 1862 )
hippa picta ( Heller, 1861 )
Hippa strigillata ( stimpson, 1860 )
hippa testudinaria ( herbst, 1791 )
hippa truncatifrons ( miers, 1878 )
It is closely सम्बन्धित to the genus emerita, and प्रजाति have often महरूम transferred between the two genera.
जकार्ता ( ), officially known as the खास पूंजी प्रदेश of जकार्ता ( ), is the capital and largest नगर of Indonesia.
Located on the northwest coast of जावा, जकार्ता is the देश 's आर्थिक, cultural और political केन्द्र, और with a जनसांख्यिकी of 10,187,595 as of November 2011, it is the सबसे populous नगर in Indonesia और in southeast Asia, और is the thirteenth most populated नगर in the संसार.
the आधिकारिक metropolitan area, known as Jabodetabek ( a नाम formed by combining the आरंभिक syllables of Jakarta, Bogor, Depok, tangerang and Bekasi ), is the दूसरी largest in the संसार, yet the metropolis 's suburbs still continue परे it.
Jakarta is सूचीबद्ध as a global city in the 2008 वैश्वीकरण and World Cities पढ़ाई Group and संजाल ( GaWC ) शोध.
and has an क्षेत्रफल of.
इस क्षेत्रफल रै population of well over 28 लाख, making it one of the संसार 's largest conurbations in शर्तें of number of निवासियों.
In 2011, Jakarta क्रमित 17th among the संसार 's 200 largest शहरों, a जम्प इससे इसके 2007 ranking of 171.
Jakarta has grown more rapidly than Kuala lumpur, Beijing and Bangkok.
Established in the चौथी century, the नगर became an महत्वपूर्ण व्यापार बंदरगाहों लिये the Kingdom of sunda.
it थी the de facto capital of the Dutch East इंडीज ( जब it थी known as Batavia ) और रै जारी as the capital of Indonesia चूंकि the देश 's स्वतंत्रता was घोषित in 1945.
The नगर is the सीट of the ASEAN सचिवालय.
जकार्ता is परोसा by the soekarno–hatta International Airport, Halim perdanakusuma International Airport, और Tanjung priok harbour ; it is connected by अनेक intercity and commuter railways, and परोसा by अनेक bus lines कार्यशील on सुरक्षित busways.
a ठेठ घर एयर conditioning खिड़की ईकाई.
Air conditioning is the process of altering the गुण of air ( primarily तापमान and humidity ) to अधिक favourable शर्तें.
More generally, एयर conditioning can refer to कोई रूप of technological कूलिंग, हीटिंग, वेंटिलेशन, or कीटाणुशोधन that modifies the कंडीशन of air.
an एयर conditioner ( प्रायः referred to as एयर con, ac or A/C, and नहीं to be confused with the संक्षिप्त for alternating वर्तमान ) is a प्रमुख or घर appliance, प्रणाली, or यांत्रिकी designed to change the एयर तापमान और आर्द्रता within an area ( used लिये कूलिंग and sometimes heating depending on the air गुण at a दिए time ).
the cooling is typically किया using a simple प्रशीतन cycle, but sometimes evaporation is प्रयुक्त, commonly लिये सुकून कूलिंग in buildings और मोटर वाहनों.
in निर्माण, a complete प्रणाली of heating, ventilation और air conditioning is referred to as `` HVAC ``.

dc Talk ( styled as dc बात ), is a Grammy -winning ईसाई रैप तिकड़ी.

the बाइबल is a compilation of many shorter books written at अलग टाइम्स और बाद assembled into the biblical canon.
All लकिन the shortest of ये किताबे have महरूम divided into अध्याय, generally a पेज or so in length, चूंकि the early 13th century.
चूंकि the mid-16th सदी, each अध्याय रै been further divided into `` verses '' of a few short lines or वाक्य.
Sometimes a वाक्य spans more than एक श्लोक, as in the मामला of, और sometimes वहीँ is अधिक than one वाक्य in a सिंगल श्लोक, as in the मामला of.
as the chapter and श्लोक विभाजन were नहीं भाग of the original ग्रन्थ, वे form part of the paratext of the Bible.
The यहूदी divisions of the यहूदी टेक्स्ट differ at विभिन्न अंक इससे those प्रयुक्त by ईसाइयों.
For उदाहरण, in यहूदी परंपरा, the ascriptions to many ज़बूर हैं regarded as स्वतंत्र verses, बनाना 116 more verses, whereas the established Christian अभ्यास is to गिनती and क्रमांक प्रत्येक psalm ascription साथ साथ the first verse following it.
कुछ अध्याय divisions भी occur in अलग स्थान, e.g. in Hebrew bibles is numbered as in ईसाई अनुवाद.
an अनुक्रमणिका ( बहुवचन : indexes ) is a सूची of शब्द or वाक्यांश ( 'headings ' ) और संबद्ध pointers ( 'लोकेटरs ' ) to जहाँ useful material relating to कि heading can be found in a document.
In a परंपरागत back-of-the-book अनुक्रमणिका the headings होगा include names of people, स्थान और कार्यक्रम, और अवधारणाओं चयनित by a person as होने प्रासंगिक and of ब्याज to a संभावित reader of the book.
the pointers हैं typically पेज numbers, paragraph numbers or खण्ड संख्याएँ.
In a पुस्तकालयों कैटलॉग the शब्द हैं authors, शीर्षक, विषय headings, etc., और the संकेतक हैं कॉल numbers.
अंतरजाल ढूंढें इंजन, ऐसे as google, and full text searching help provide access to सूचना लकिन are नहीं as selective as an अनुक्रमणिका, as वे provide non-relevant कड़ी, और may मिस relevant सूचना if it is नहीं phrased in exactly the way वे expect.
in United राज्य वित्तीय विनियमन, a संदिग्ध activity रपट ( or SAR ) is a रपट बना by a वित्तीय संस्था to the Financial अपराधों Enforcement संजाल ( fincen ), an agency of the संयुक्त States विभाग of the Treasury, regarding suspicious or potentially संदिग्ध activity.

फेसबुक is an ऑनलाइन सोशल networking सेवा, जिनकी नाम तना from the colloquial नाम लिये the किताब दिए to students at the start of the academic साल by some university administrations in the United राज्य to help students मिलेंगी to know each अन्य.

The जालस्थल 's सदस्यता थी initially limited by the संस्थापकों to हार्वर्ड students, लकिन was expanded to अन्य कॉलेजों in the बोस्टन area, the आइवी लीग, and स्टैनफोर्ड University.
it gradually added support लिये विद्यार्थी at विभिन्न अन्य विश्वविद्यालयों before opening to high स्कूल विद्यार्थी, and eventually to anyone aged 13 और over.
फेसबुक now allows कोई उपयोक्ता जो declare themselves to be at तनिक 13 years बूढ़ा to become registered उपयोक्ता of the साईट.
उपयोक्ता must register before using the साईट, बाद जिससे they may create a निजी profile, add अन्य users as मित्रों, and एक्सचेंज संदेश, including स्वचालित सूचनाएं when वे अद्यतन their प्रोफ़ाइल.
additionally, उपयोक्ता may join common-interest user groups, व्यवस्थित by कार्यस्थल, स्कूल or कॉलेज, or अन्य विशेषताएँ, और categorize उनके friends into सूचियाँ such as `` लोगों From कार्य '' or `` Close Friends ''.
as of सितंबर 2012, फेसबुक रै over एक billion क्रियाशील users.
According to a may 2011 उपभोक्ता रिपोर्ट्स survey, वहीँ हैं 7.5 million children अंतर्गत 13 with accounts and 5 million अंतर्गत 10, violating the साईट 's शर्तें of सेवा.

a जनवरी 2009 compete.com study क्रमित Facebook as the most प्रयुक्त सोशल networking सेवा by विश्वव्यापी monthly active users.
entertainment साप्ताहिक शामिल the साईट on इसके end-of-the-decade `` best-of '' सूची, saying, `` How on धरती did we stalk हमारी exes, remember हमारी co-workers ' birthdays, bug our मित्रों, और खेल a rousing खेल of scrabulous पहले Facebook ? ''
आलोचकों, ऐसे as Facebook Detox, state कि Facebook रै turned into a नेशनल obsession in the United राज्य, resulting in विशाल amounts of समय lost और प्रोत्साहित आत्ममोह.

According to Social Media Today, in अप्रैल 2010 an अनुमानित 41.6 % ( 129.5 लाख ) of the U.S. जनसांख्यिकी था a Facebook account.
nevertheless, फेसबुक 's मार्केट विकास started to stall in some regions, साथ the site खोने 7 million active users in the संयुक्त राज्य और Canada in may 2011.
Facebook आखिरकार दायर लिये an initial public offering on February 1, 2012, and थी headquartered in Menlo Park, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.

Sulfonamide कार्यात्मक समूह
Hydrochlorothiazide is a sulfonamide और a thiazide.
furosemide is a sulfonamide, लकिन नहीं a thiazide.
सल्फोनेमाइड or sulphonamide is the आधार of अनेक समूह of drugs.
the original जीवाणुरोधी sulfonamides ( sometimes पुकारा sulfa दवाएँ or sulpha दवाएँ ) हैं synthetic रोगाणुरोधी एजेंटों कि contain the सल्फोनेमाइड समूह.
Some sulfonamides हैं भी विहीन of antibacterial activity, e.g., the anticonvulsant sultiame.
The sulfonylureas and thiazide diuretics हैं नए drug समूह आधारित on the antibacterial sulfonamides.
sulfa allergies are आम, hence medications containing sulfonamides are prescribed carefully.
It is महत्वपूर्ण to मेक a भेद between sulfa दवाएँ और other sulfur-containing दवाएँ and additives, ऐसे as sulfates and sulfites, which हैं chemically unrelated to the sulfonamide समूह, और do नहीं cause the वही hypersensitivity प्रतिक्रियाएँ देखी in the sulfonamides.

The नई यॉर्क यात्री Ship टर्मिनल ( भी ज्ञात as the Luxury Liner पंक्ति or Manhattan क्रूज टर्मिनल or नई यॉर्क क्रूज टर्मिनल ) is a terminal for ocean-going passenger जहाजों on मैनहटन 's वेस्ट side.
the टर्मिनल consists of North नदी Piers 88, 90, 92 and 94 on the Hudson नदी between वेस्ट 46th and वेस्ट 54th Street.
( As a सामान्य नियम, pier numbers in मैनहटन can be संकल्पित by adding 40 to the corresponding cross-street. )
जहाजों अभी डॉक at Piers 88, 90 and 92.

the नगर is forecasting कि 1.5 लाख होगा उपयोग the terminal by 2017.
The पियर are long and apart.
वे were first completed in 1935 to replace the चेल्सी पियर as the नगर 's लक्ज़री liner terminal.
The new terminal थी built to हैंडल bigger जहाजों कि था outgrown the चेल्सी पियर.
the पियर यहूद संवर in 1970 और हैं फिलहाल undergoing another $ 150 लाख renovation.
the renovated योजनाएँ call for it to handle तीन large ships at a समय.
In doing renovations, the नगर is भी considering decommissioning बांध 92.

ईसाई सही is a term प्रयुक्त in the United States to describe right-wing Christian राजनैतिक समूह कि हैं characterized by उनके दमदार support of socially conservative policies.
Christian conservatives प्रधानतया तलाश to लागू उनके समझना of the teachings of christianity to राजनीती और public policy by proclaiming the मान of those शिक्षाओं and/or by seeking to उपयोग those teachings to influence law और पब्लिक policy.
in the U.S., the Christian सही is an informal गठबन्धन formed around a core of धर्मान्तरण protestants कि draws `` support इससे नीतियां conservative catholics, Jews, mormons, and occasionally secularists '' who share their लक्ष्य.
the गति रै its roots in अमरीकी politics going back as far the 1940s और रै महरूम विशेषकर influential चूंकि the 1970s.
उनके influence draws, in part, from grassroots activism as खूब as their फ़ोकस on सोशल issues और ability to motivate the electorate around those issues.
The Christian right is notable today for advancing socially conservative positions on मुद्दे सहित स्कूल prayer, स्टेम कोशिका शोध, समलैंगिकता, contraception, गर्भपात, और pornography.
हालांकि the ईसाई right is usually associated with the u.S., the गति has been a कुंजी factor in the राजनीती of Canada, The नीदरलैंड्स, Northern आयरलैंड और ऑस्ट्रेलिया, among अन्य.

lr44 is the आईईसी नामांकन लिये an alkaline 1.5 volt बटन कोशिका, commonly प्रयुक्त in small led flashlights, digital thermometers, calculators, calipers, watches, clocks, toys और लेज़र संकेतक.
LR44 क्षारीय कोशिका
The बैटरी nomenclature is पारिभाषित by the अंतरराष्ट्रीय विद्युततकनीकी Commission ( आईईसी ) in इसके 60086-3 मानक ( प्राथमिक बैटरी, भाग 3 देखें batteries ).
The अक्षर L indicates the electrochemical प्रणाली प्रयुक्त ; a जस्ता negative एलेक्ट्रोड, manganese डाइऑक्साइड depolarizer और positive electrode, and an alkaline electrolyte.
r44 indicates a गोलाकार कोशिका 11.4±0.2 mm व्यास और 5.2±0.2 mm ऊँचाई as defined by the IEC मानक 60086.

Formerly, mercury बैटरी were बना as button cells ( प्रकार MR44 और nr44 ).
zinc-air बैटरी type pr44 आवश्यकता एयर to work.
