hurricane Katrina थी the deadliest and सबसे destructive अटलांटिक hurricane of the 2005 अटलांटिक hurricane season.
It was the costliest प्राकृतिक विपत्ति, as खूब as one of the पाँच deadliest hurricanes, in the इतिहास of the संयुक्त States.
among recorded Atlantic hurricanes, it थी the sixth strongest overall.
at तनिक 1,833 people died in the hurricane and subsequent floods, बनाना it the deadliest U.S. hurricane since the 1928 okeechobee hurricane ; कुल property क्षति was अनुमानित at $ 81 अरब ( 2005 USD ), nearly ट्रिपल the क्षति brought by hurricane एंड्रयू in 1992.
hurricane Katrina formed over the बहामा on अगस्त 23, 2005 और crossed southern Florida as a मॉडरेट श्रेणी 1 hurricane, causing some मौतों and बाढ़ वहीँ पहले strengthening rapidly in the गल्फ of मैक्सिको.
the hurricane strengthened to a श्रेणी 5 hurricane over the गरम गल्फ water, लकिन weakened पहले making इसके दूसरी landfall as a Category 3 hurricane on the morning of सोमवार, August 29 in southeast louisiana.
It caused कठोर destruction along the गल्फ coast from सेंट्रल फ्लोरिडा to टेक्सास, much of it due to the तूफ़ान surge.
the सबसे significant क्रमांक of deaths occurred in New ऑरलियन्स, Louisiana, जिससे flooded as the तटबन्ध प्रणाली catastrophically failed, in अनेक मामले घंटों बाद the storm था स्थानांतरित अंतर्देशीय.
Eventually 80 % of the city and large tracts of neighboring parishes became flooded, and the floodwaters lingered for weeks.
however, the worst property damage occurred in coastal areas, ऐसे as सब Mississippi beachfront कस्बों, जिससे were flooded over 90 % in घंटों, as नौकाएँ और कसीनो barges rammed buildings, pushing गाड़ियाँ और houses अंतर्देशीय, साथ waters reaching 6–12 मील ( 10–19 km ) इससे the बीच.
the hurricane surge सुरक्षा असफलताओं in नई Orleans हैं considered the worst civil अभियान्त्रिकी विपत्ति in u.S. इतिहास और prompted a मुकदमा विरूद्ध the U.S. Army corps of Engineers ( USACE ), the designers and builders of the levee प्रणाली as mandated by the बाढ़ कंट्रोल अधिनियम of 1965.
जिम्मेदारी for the असफलताओं and बाढ़ थी रखी squarely on the Army corps in जनवरी 2008 by न्यायधीश stanwood Duval, U.S. District अदालत, but the संघीय एजेंसी could not be held financially liable due to sovereign immunity in the बाढ़ कंट्रोल Act of 1928.
वहीँ was भी an छानबीन of the प्रतिक्रियाएँ from federal, state और लोकल governments, resulting in the resignation of संघीय Emergency Management Agency ( FEMA ) निदेशक Michael D. भूरा, और of नई ऑरलियन्स Police Department ( nopd ) Superintendent एडी कम्पास.
अनेक एजेंसियों including the United States coast Guard ( USCG ), नेशनल Hurricane बीच ( nhc ), and National मौसम सेवा ( nws ) were commended लिये उनके क्रियाएँ.
वे provided सटीक hurricane मौसम tracking forecasts साथ sufficient lead समय.
भी the most insistent appeals इससे नेशनल, राज्य और लोकल पब्लिक officials to residents to evacuate before the storm किया not warn कि the levees could उल्लंघन और fail.
u.S. कर्ज़ इससे 1940 to 2011.
Red लाइनों indicate the `` कर्ज़ आयोजित by the public '' and ब्लैक लाइनों indicate the total नेशनल कर्ज़ or सकल public कर्ज़.
the अंतर is the `` intragovernmental कर्ज़, '' जिससे शामिल obligations to सरकारी programs such as Social Security.
Stated as a formula, National कर्ज़ = कर्ज़ आयोजित by the Public + intragovernmental कर्ज़.
The दूसरी फलक shows the two debt आंकड़े as a percentage of U.S. जीडीपी ( डालर मान of U.S. आर्थिक उत्पादन for that साल ).
The top फलक is deflated so every year is in 2010 डॉलर.
the संयुक्त राज्य पब्लिक कर्ज़ is the money उधार by the संघीय government of the United राज्य through the issuing of securities by the राजकोष और अन्य संघीय government agencies.
us public debt consists of दो components:
कर्ज़ held by the पब्लिक शामिल राजकोष securities आयोजित by investors बाहर the federal government, सहित that आयोजित by individuals, corporations, the Federal Reserve प्रणाली and विदेशी, राज्य and local governments.
कर्ज़ held by government accounts or intragovernmental debt includes non-marketable Treasury प्रतिभूति आयोजित in खाते administered by the संघीय सरकारी that are owed to कार्यक्रम beneficiaries, such as the सोशल Security Trust Fund.
कर्ज़ आयोजित by government accounts represents the cumulative surpluses, including ब्याज आय, of these accounts कि have been invested in राजकोष प्रतिभूति.
Public debt increases or decreases as a result of the annual एकीकृत budget deficit or surplus.
The संघीय सरकारी budget deficit or surplus is the अंतर between सरकारी receipts और बिता, ignoring intra-governmental हस्तांतरण.
however, some spending that is excluded इससे the deficit ( supplemental appropriations ) also adds to the कर्ज़.
historically, the US पब्लिक कर्ज़ as a share of जीडीपी increased during युद्धों and recessions, और subsequently अस्वीकृत.
लिये example, कर्ज़ आयोजित by the पब्लिक as a share of जीडीपी peaked बस बाद World War ii ( 113 % of जीडीपी in 1945 ), लकिन तब fell over the following 30 सालो.
In recent दशकों, however, विशाल बजट deficits and the resulting increases in debt have led to चिंता परिचय the long-term sustainability of the संघीय सरकारी 's फिस्कल policies.
on 2 अप्रैल 2013, कर्ज़ held by the public थी approximately $ 11.959 trillion or about 75 % of जीडीपी.
intragovernmental holdings stood at $ 4.846 खरब, giving a combined total पब्लिक debt of $ 16.805 खरब.
as of जनवरी 2013, $ 5.6 खरब or approximately 47 % of the कर्ज़ आयोजित by the public was स्वामित्व by विदेशी निवेशकों, the largest of जिससे were the People 's गणतंत्र of चीन और Japan at बस over $ 1.1 खरब प्रत्येक.
in basketball, an assist is attributed to a खिलाड़ी who गुजरता the बॉल to a teammate in a way कि leads to a स्कोर by फ़ील्ड लक्ष्य, अर्थ that he or वो was `` assisting '' in the basket.
There is some निर्णय शामिल in deciding whether a passer should be credited with an assist.
An assist can be scored for the passer भी if the खिलाड़ी जो receives the pass makes a basket बाद dribbling the बॉल.
However, the असली परिभाषा of an assist किया नहीं include such situations, so the comparison of assist आंकडे across eras is a जटिल matter.
तभी the pass directly पहले the स्कोर may be counted as an assist, so no अधिक than one assist can be recorded प्रति फ़ील्ड goal ( unlike in अन्य खेल, such as ice हॉकी ).
A pass कि leads to a shooting बेईमानी and स्कोरिंग by फ़्री throws करता नहीं गिनती as an assist in the एनबीए, but does in FIBA खेल ( तभी one assist is awarded प्रति नियत of फ़्री throws in जिससे at least एक free throw is बना ).
पाइंट गार्ड tend to get the सबसे assists प्रति खेल ( apg ), as उनके भूमिका is primarily कि of a passer and ballhandler.
centers tend to get fewer assists, लकिन centers साथ good मंजिल उपस्थिति और court दृष्टि can dominate a team by assisting.
Being अंदर the कुंजी, the बीच often has the best कोण और the बेहतरीन स्थिति लिये `` बर्तन '' and अन्य छोटी गुजरता in the scoring क्षेत्रफल.
बीच wilt चेम्बरलेन led the NBA in assists in 1968.
a strong बीच साथ inside-scoring prowess, such as पूर्व एनबीए बीच hakeem Olajuwon, can also be an प्रभावी assistor because the defense 's double-teaming tends to खोलें up ठोकर in the रूप of shooters.
the एनबीए single-game assist रिकार्ड is 30, आयोजित by Scott skiles of the Orlando जादू विरूद्ध the डेनवर टेंडर्स, on दिसम्बर 30, 1990.
The NBA रिकार्ड लिये सबसे career assists is held by John Stockton साथ 15,806.
the मिल or mille ( ) ( sometimes mil in the UK, when discussing property कर in the संयुक्त राज्य, or previously in साइप्रस and Malta ) is a now-abstract unit of currency used sometimes in हिसाब.
in the संयुक्त States, it is a notional ईकाई समतुल्य to of a United राज्य डालर ( a tenth of a cent ).
in the संयुक्त किंगडम it was proposed दौरान the दशकों of discussion on the decimalization of the pound as a division of the पाउंड sterling.
Several अन्य currencies प्रयुक्त the mill, ऐसे as the maltese लीरा.
the पद comes इससे the लैटिन `` millesimum '', meaning `` thousandth part ''.
The Greco-Persian युद्धों ( also प्रायः पुकारा the Persian युद्धों ) were a श्रेणी of विरोध between the हख़ामनी Empire of फारस और city-states of the Hellenic संसार कि प्रारंभ in 499 bc और lasted जबतक 449 BC.
the टक्कर between the fractious राजनैतिक संसार of the यूनानियों और the विशाल साम्राज्य of the फारसियों began जब सायरस the Great conquered ionia in 547 BC.
Struggling to rule the independent-minded शहरों of ionia, the Persians appointed उत्पीड़क to rule प्रत्येक of उन्हें.
इस होता prove to be the सोर्स of much trouble लिये the Greeks and फारसियों alike.
in 499 bc, the तब tyrant of Miletus, aristagoras, embarked on an expedition to जीतें the island of Naxos, साथ पारसी support ; however, the expedition थी a क़हर और, pre-empting उसके dismissal, aristagoras incited सब of हैलेनिक एशिया नाबालिग into rebellion विरूद्ध the फारसियों.
इस थी the beginning of the Ionian विद्रोह, जिससे होता पिछला जबतक 493 bc, progressively आरेखण अधिक regions of एशिया नाबालिग into the विरोध.
Aristagoras secured military support इससे एथेंस और eretria, और in 498 bc ये शक्तियां helped to कैप्चर और burn the Persian क्षेत्रीय पूंजी of Sardis.
the Persian किंग Darius the ग्रेट vowed to have बदला on एथेंस और eretria लिये इस act.
The revolt जारी, साथ the two पहलू effectively stalemated throughout 497–495 bc.
in 494 bc, the फारसियों regrouped, and attacked the epicentre of the revolt in Miletus.
At the Battle of lade, the ionians suffered a निर्णायक defeat, and the विद्रोह collapsed, साथ the फाइनल members होने stamped out the following साल.
seeking to सुरक्षित उसके साम्राज्य इससे further revolts and from the हस्तक्षेप of the मेनलैंड यूनानियों, दारा embarked on a scheme to जीतें यूनानियों and to सजा एथेंस and Eretria लिये burning Sardis.
The पहला पारसी आक्रमण of यूनानियों began in 492 bc, साथ the पारसी general mardonius conquering Thrace और Macedon पहले अनेक mishaps forced an जल्दी समाप्त to the अभियान.
in 490 BC a दूसरी फ़ोर्स was sent to यूनानियों, इस समय across the Aegean Sea, अंतर्गत the कमांड of Datis और artaphernes.
This expedition subjugated the cyclades, पहले besieging, capturing and razing Eretria.
However, जबकि en route to attack एथेंस, the पारसी फ़ोर्स थी decisively पराजित by the athenians at the बैटल of Marathon, समाप्ति Persian प्रयत्न लिये the समय होने.
दारा तब began to plan to पूरा the conquest of यूनानियों, but died in 486 BC और जिम्मेदारी लिये the conquest passed to his son xerxes i.
In 480 BC, Xerxes personally led the second पारसी आक्रमण of यूनानियों with एक of the largest प्राचीन armies ever assembled.
Victory over the 'allied ' यूनानी राज्य ( led by Sparta और Athens ) at the बैटल of thermopylae अनुमत the फारसियों to torch एथेंस and overrun most of Greece.
however, while seeking to destroy the संयुक्त यूनानी बेड़े, the फारसियों suffered a severe शिकस्त at the बैटल of salamis.
The following साल, the confederated यूनानियों गई on the offensive, defeating the Persian army at the बैटल of plataea, and समाप्ति the आक्रमण of Greece.
the allied Greeks followed up their कामयाबी by destroying the बाकी of the पारसी बेड़े at the बैटल of mycale, before expelling पारसी garrisons from sestos ( 479 bc ) और Byzantium ( 478 BC ).
the क्रियाएँ of the general pausanias at the घेरा of byzantium alienated अनेक of the यूनानी राज्य इससे the spartans, और the anti-Persian गठबंधन थी इसलिए reconstituted around Athenian नेतृत्व, as the so-called delian League.
The delian लीग continued to अभियान विरूद्ध Persia लिये the next तीन दशकों, शुरूआत साथ the expulsion of the बाकी पारसी garrisons इससे यूरोपीय.
At the Battle of the Eurymedon in 466 BC, the लीग won a दोगुना victory कि finally secured स्वतंत्रता लिये the cities of ionia.
however, the League 's भागीदारी in an Egyptian revolt ( इससे 460–454 BC ) resulted in a विनाशकारी शिकस्त, और further campaigning थी suspended.
a बेड़े was भेजा to साइप्रस in 451 bc, लकिन achieved छोटी, और when it withdrew the Greco-Persian Wars खींचा to a quiet end.
कुछ historical sources सुझाएँ the end of hostilities was marked by a सलाम सन्धि between एथेंस और फारस, the so-called Peace of callias.
hooverville निकट पोर्टलैंड, ऑरेगॉन
A `` hooverville '' is the popular नाम लिये shanty कस्बों built by बेघर people during the ग्रेट Depression.
They यहूद नामित after Herbert हूवर, जो थी अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States दौरान the onset of the अवसाद and widely blamed for it.
The पद was coined by Charles माइकेल्सन, publicity chief of the Democratic नेशनल कमेटी.
Matthew माइकल hasselbeck ( born सितंबर 25, 1975 ) is an अमरीकी football quarterback लिये the इंडियानापोलिस Colts of the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल League ( एनएफएल ).
He थी drafted in the छठे गोलाकार of the 1998 एनएफएल Draft by the Green खाड़ी Packers.
बाद a ऋतु on the अभ्यास squad और two सीज़न backing up ब्रेट Favre, he थी traded to the Seattle Seahawks in 2001.
Hasselbeck gained the starting role in 2003, और led सिएटल to छह playoff दिखावे और a सुपर Bowl रूप ; he थी चयनित to तीन प्रो Bowls and an all-pro चयन.
Following टेन seasons साथ the सीहॉक्स, hasselbeck joined the टेनेसी Titans in 2011.
Hasselbeck then signed a अनुबंध साथ the इंडियानापोलिस कोल्टस in 2013 कम than 24 hours बाद being released by the टेनेसी Titans.
आईसीटी is inevitably सम्बन्धित to the कंप्यूटर संजाल.
Information और Communications प्रौद्योगिकी or ( आईसीटी ), is प्रायः used as an विस्तारित पर्याय लिये information technology ( it ), लकिन is a अधिक specific term कि stresses the भूमिका of एकीकृत communications and the integration of telecommunications ( telephone lines और wireless सिग्नल ), computers as well as जरुरी एंटरप्राइज़ तन्त्र, middleware, भंडार, और audio-visual systems, जिससे enable उपयोक्ता to access, स्टोर, transmit, और manipulate सूचना.
the phrase ICT था महरूम प्रयुक्त by अकादमिक शोधकर्ताओं चूंकि the 1980s, but it became popular बाद it was used in a रपट to the uk सरकारी by डेनिस stevenson in 1997 and in the संशोधित नेशनल Curriculum लिये England, वेल्स और उत्तरी Ireland in 2000.
the term आईसीटी is now भी प्रयुक्त to refer to the convergence of audio-visual और telephone संजाल with कंप्यूटर संजाल through a single cabling or कड़ी प्रणाली.
There हैं विशाल आर्थिक प्रोत्साहन ( विशाल लागत savings due to विलोपन of the टेलीफोन network ) to merge the audio-visual, building प्रबन्धन और टेलीफोन संजाल साथ the computer संजाल system using a सिंगल एकीकृत प्रणाली of cabling, सिग्नल distribution और management.
The term infocommunications is प्रयुक्त in some cases as a shorter रूप of information और communication ( s ) प्रौद्योगिकी.
in फैक्ट infocommunications is the expansion of telecommunications with information प्रसंस्करण and सामग्री handling कृत्यों on a common digital प्रौद्योगिकी आधार.
For a तुलना of these and अन्य शर्तें, see.

A schematic presentation of the प्लम खीर model of the atom ; in Thomson 's गणितीय model the `` corpuscles '' ( or modern electrons ) यहूद arranged non-randomly, in घूर्णन rings
The वर्तमान model of the sub-atomic structure involves a घना केंद्रक surrounded by a probabilistic `` cloud '' of electrons
the प्लम खीर model of the atom by J. J. thomson, जो discovered the electron in 1897, was प्रस्तावित in 1904 before the discovery of the परमाणु केंद्रक in अनुक्रम to add the इलेक्ट्रॉन to the परमाणु मॉडल.
In this मॉडल, the atom is रचित of electrons ( जिससे Thomson स्टिल called `` corpuscles '', हालांकि G. J. Stoney had प्रस्तावित कि atoms of electricity be पुकारा electrons in 1894 ) घिरी by a सूप of positive charge to balance the electrons ' ऋणात्मक charges, like negatively charged `` plums `` घिरी by positively चार्ज `` खीर ``.
The electrons ( as we know them today ) यहूद विचार to be positioned throughout the atom, लकिन साथ अनेक structures possible लिये positioning अनेक electrons, particularly घूर्णन rings of electrons ( see below ).
बजाय of a सूप, the अणु थी also sometimes कहा to have had a `` बादल '' of positive charge.
साथ इस मॉडल, Thomson abandoned उसके earlier `` nebular अणु '' hypothesis in जिससे the atom was रचित of immaterial vortices.
अभी, at least भाग of the atom थी to be रचित of thomson 's particulate negative corpuscles, हालांकि the बाकी of the positively चार्ज part of the अणु remained somewhat nebulous and ill-defined.
the 1904 thomson model थी disproved by the 1909 सुनहरा foil प्रयोग of hans Geiger और Ernest Marsden.
This थी interpreted by अर्नेस्ट Rutherford in 1911
to imply a बहुत छोटी nucleus of the अणु containing a बहुत high positive charge ( in the मामला of gold, enough to balance about 100 electrons ), thus अग्रणी to the Rutherford model of the atom.
हालांकि सुनहरा रै an परमाणु क्रमांक of 79, तत्काल बाद रदरफोर्ड 's पेपर appeared in 1911 antonius Van डेन Broek made the intuitive suggestion कि परमाणु क्रमांक is nuclear चार्ज.
the matter required experiment to decide.
Henry moseley 's work दिखाया experimentally in 1913 ( देखिए Moseley 's law ) that the effective नाभिकीय चार्ज थी बहुत बंद to the atomic number ( moseley मिला only one ईकाई अंतर ), और moseley referenced तभी the papers of Van डेन Broek and Rutherford.
This कार्य culminated in the solar-system-like ( लकिन quantum-limited ) bohr मॉडल of the अणु in the वही year, in which a केंद्रक containing an atomic क्रमांक of positive charge is घिरी by an बराबर number of electrons in कक्षीय शेल.
bohr था also प्रेरित moseley 's work.
Thomson 's मॉडल थी compared ( हालांकि नहीं by Thomson ) to a British मिठाई पुकारा plum खीर, hence the name.
thomson 's पेपर was प्रकाशित in the कूच 1904 संस्करण of the Philosophical पत्रिका, the अग्रणी अंग्रेजों विज्ञान जर्नल of the day.
in thomson 's view :... the atoms of the elements consist of a number of negatively electrified corpuscles enclosed in a गोला of uniform positive विद्युतीकरण,...
in इस model, the electrons were फ़्री to rotate भीतर the blob or बादल of धनात्मक पदार्थ.
These orbits यहूद stabilized in the model by the फैक्ट कि जब an इलेक्ट्रॉन स्थानांतरित दूर from the बीच of the धनात्मक cloud, it felt a larger net positive inward फ़ोर्स, क्युकी वहीँ was अधिक सामग्री of विपरीत charge, अंदर इसके कक्षा ( see Gauss 's law ).
In thomson 's model, electrons यहूद फ़्री to rotate in बजती जिससे were further stabilized by interactions between the electrons, और spectra were to be accounted लिये by उर्जा मतभेद of different रिंग orbits.
Thomson attempted to मेक his मॉडल account लिये some of the प्रमुख spectral lines ज्ञात for कुछ तत्व, लकिन was नहीं notably successful at इस.
स्टिल, thomson 's मॉडल ( साथ with a समान saturnian रिंग मॉडल for परमाणु electrons, भी put आगे in 1904 by Nagaoka बाद जेम्स क्लर्क मैक्सवेल 's मॉडल of शनि 's बजती ), were पहले harbingers of the later and more successful solar-system-like bohr मॉडल of the atom.
ठेठ स्ट्रिप of बेकन.
बेकन is a cured meat prepared इससे a सुअर.
it is first cured using विशाल quantities of salt, either in a brine or in a dry पैकिंग ; the result is भैस bacon ( भी ज्ञात as ग्रीन bacon ).
Fresh bacon may तब be further सूखी लिये weeks or महीने in ठंडा एयर, or it may be boiled or smoked.
Fresh और सूखी bacon is typically पकाया पहले eating.
boiled बेकन is तैयार to खा, as is कुछ स्मोक्ड बेकन, but may be पकाया further पहले eating.
बेकन is prepared from अनेक अलग cuts of meat.
it is usually made from side and वापस कटौती of pork, मगर in the संयुक्त राज्य, where it is लगभग सदा prepared from पोर्क belly ( typically referred to as `` streaky '', `` वसीय '', or `` अमरीकी style '' outside of the US and कनाडा ).
the पक्ष काटें has अधिक meat और less मोटे than the belly.
बेकन may be prepared from either of two distinct वापस कटौती : fatback, which is लगभग pure fat, और पोर्क loin, जिससे is very झुकना.
bacon-cured पोर्क loin is known as वापस बेकन.
uncooked पोर्क belly बेकन strips.
Bacon may be eaten स्मोक्ड, boiled, fried, baked, or ग्रील्ड, or प्रयुक्त as a नाबालिग संघटक to स्वाद dishes.
Bacon is भी प्रयुक्त for barding और larding roasts, especially खेल, e.g. venison, pheasant.
the word is निकला इससे the Old ऊँची जर्मनी bacho, meaning `` buttock '', `` हैम '' or `` side of बेकन '', and cognate साथ the Old French बेकन.
In महाद्वीपीय यूरोपीय, इस भाग of the सुअर is usually नहीं स्मोक्ड जैसे बेकन is in the United राज्य ; it is प्रयुक्त primarily in cubes ( lardons ) as a कुकिंग ingredient, valued दोनो as a source of मोटे और लिये its स्वाद.
in Italy, this is पुकारा pancetta और is प्रायः पकाया in छोटी घन or परोसा uncooked और thinly sliced as part of an antipasto.
मांस from other animals, ऐसे as बीफ, lamb, मुर्गा, goat, or तुर्कों, may भी be काटें, cured, or वरना prepared to resemble bacon, and may भी be referred to as `` बेकन ''.
Such use is आम in areas साथ significant यहूदी and मुस्लिम populations.
The यूएसडीए defines bacon as `` the cured पेट of a swine carcass '' ; other कटौती और characteristics जरूर be separately योग्य ( e.g., `` smoked pork loin बेकन '' ).
For सुरक्षा, बेकन जरूर be treated to prevent trichinosis, caused by Trichinella, a parasitic roundworm जिससे can be destroyed by heating, जमने, drying, or smoking.
Bacon is विशिष्ट from salt पोर्क और हैम by differences in the brine ( or शुष्क पैकिंग ).
Bacon brine रै added curing ingredients, सबसे notably सोडियम nitrite, और occasionally सोडियम नाइट्रेट or potassium नाइट्रेट ( साल्टपीटर ) ; sodium ascorbate or erythorbate हैं added to accelerate curing और stabilize रंग.
flavorings ऐसे as brown शुगर or मेपल are used for कुछ products.
if प्रयुक्त, sodium polyphosphates are added to improve sliceability and reduce spattering जब the bacon is पण fried.
आज, a brine लिये हैम, but नहीं bacon, शामिल a विशाल राशि of शुगर.
Historically, `` हैम '' और `` बेकन '' referred to different कटौती of मांस that यहूद brined or packed identically, प्रायः साथ in the वही बैरल.
the कर्मचारी रिटायरमेंट आय सुरक्षा Act of 1974 ( erisa ) (, codified in भाग at ) is a संघीय विधि जिससे establishes minimum मानकों लिये पेंशन योजनाएँ in निजी industry and provides for extensive नियम on the federal आय कर effects of ट्रांजेक्शन associated with employee लाभ योजनाएँ.
erisa थी enacted to protect the रूचि of कर्मचारी लाभ योजना भागीदार और their beneficiaries by:
Requiring the disclosure of financial और अन्य information concerning the योजना to beneficiaries ;
establishing मानकों of conduct लिये योजना fiduciaries ;
Providing for उचित remedies and अभिगम to the federal न्यायालयों.
erisa is sometimes प्रयुक्त to refer to the full देह of laws regulating employee benefit योजनाएँ, which हैं मिला mainly in the आतंरिक Revenue Code and erisa itself.
जिम्मेदारी for the निर्वचन and enforcement of erisa is divided among the विभाग of मजदूर, the Department of the राजकोष ( particularly the आतंरिक आय Service ), और the पेंशन Benefit guaranty Corporation.
illegal आव्रजन to the United राज्य is the act of विदेशी नागरिकों प्रवेश the United राज्य, without government अनुमति and in उल्लंघन of United राज्य nationality law, or staying beyond the termination तिथि of a वीज़ा, also in violation of the law.

The undocumented अप्रवासी जनसांख्यिकी of the संयुक्त राज्य in 2008 was अनुमानित by the बीच लिये Immigration Studies to be about 11 लाख people, bas from 12.5 लाख लोगों in 2007.
अन्य estimates range from 7 to 20 million.
according to a 2005 pew हिस्पैनिक Center report, 56 % of undocumented immigrants यहूद from मैक्सिको ; 22 % यहूद इससे other लैटिन अमरीकी countries ; 13 % were इससे Asia ; 6 % यहूद from यूरोपीय and कनाडा ; और 3 % were from Africa and the बाकी of the world.
Alvin स्वतंत्र स्कूल ज़िला is a school district based in एल्विन, टेक्सास ( यूएसए ).
Alvin isd is a large suburban स्कूल ज़िला दक्षिण of ह्यूस्टन in the समुदायों of Alvin, manvel, Pearland, Hillcrest, rosharon, आयोवा Colony, लिवरपूल, और Amsterdam.
AISD serves Pearland city 's rapidly growing पश्चिमी portion of the नगर including the new विशाल master-planned communities of छाया क्रीक ranch, South कांटा, and दक्षिणी Trails.

In इंसान anatomy, the ulnar nerve is a nerve जिससे रनों near the ulna अस्थि.
The ulnar collateral स्नायु of कोहनी संयुक्त is in relation with the ulnar तंत्रिका.
the तंत्रिका is the largest unprotected तंत्रिका in the इंसान body ( अर्थ unprotected by मांसपेशी or अस्थि ), so चोट is आम.
This nerve is directly कनेक्ट to the छोटी उंगली, और the सटा हाफ of the ring उंगली, supplying the palmar पक्ष of ये fingers, सहित both front और back of the tips, perhaps as दूर वापस as the fingernail beds.
एक विधि of injuring the nerve is to स्ट्राइक the medial epicondyle of the humerus इससे posteriorly, or inferiorly साथ the कोहनी flexed.
the ulnar nerve is फंस between the अस्थि और the overlying स्किन at this point.
This is commonly referred to as bumping one 's `` funny अस्थि ''.
This name is विचार to be a pun, based on the sound प्रतिरूप between the नाम of the अस्थि of the upper arm, the `` humerus `` और the word `` humorous ``.
alternatively, according to the ऑक्सफोर्ड अंग्रेज़ी Dictionary it may refer to `` the peculiar सनसनी अनुभवी जब it is struck ''.
Hogwarts School of Witchcraft और Wizardry, shortened हॉग्वार्ट्स, is a fictional अंग्रेजों स्कूल of जादू for विद्यार्थी aged ग्यारह to eighteen, और is the प्राथमिक setting for the पहला छह किताबे in j.K. Rowling 's Harry कुम्हार श्रेणी.
रोलिंग has suggested कि वो may have inadvertently लिया the नाम इससे the hogwort plant ( croton capitatus ), जिससे वो था देखी at Kew gardens some समय पहले लिखने the series, हालांकि the names `` The Hogwarts '' and `` Hoggwart '' appear in the 1954 निगेल molesworth book कैसा To be topp by geoffrey Willans.
Hogwarts स्कूल was voted as the 36th best स्कॉटिश educational स्थापना in a 2008 ऑनलाइन ranking, outranking Edinburgh 's Loretto स्कूल.
according to a निदेशक of the स्वतंत्र Schools संजाल Rankings, it थी added to the स्कूलों लिस्टिंग `` for मजा '' और was then voted on.
The u.S. subprime बंधक संकट थी a नियत of कार्यक्रम और शर्तें कि led to a वित्तीय संकट and subsequent मंदी कि began in 2008.
it was characterized by a rise in subprime बंधक delinquencies और foreclosures, और the resulting decline of प्रतिभूति समर्थित by said mortgages.
अनेक प्रमुख वित्तीय संस्थानों collapsed in सितंबर 2008, साथ significant disruption in the flow of credit to businesses और उपभोक्ता और the onset of a severe वैश्विक मंदी.
There were अनेक causes of the संकट, साथ टीकाकारों assigning different स्तर of blame to financial संस्थानों, regulators, credit agencies, government आवास policies, और उपभोक्ता, among अन्य.
a proximate कारण was the वृद्धि in subprime lending.
The प्रतिशत of lower-quality subprime mortgages originated दौरान a given साल rose इससे the ऐतिहासिक 8 % or निम्नतर range to approximately 20 % इससे 2004 to 2006, साथ much उच्चतर ratios in कुछ भाग of the U.S.
a high प्रतिशत of ये subprime mortgages, over 90 % in 2006 लिये example, were adjustable-rate mortgages.
ये two परिवर्तन यहूद भाग of a broader ट्रेंड of lowered lending standards और higher-risk बंधक उत्पाद.
further, u.S. households था become increasingly ऋणी, साथ the अनुपात of कर्ज़ to disposable निजी income उठती इससे 77 % in 1990 to 127 % at the समाप्त of 2007, much of this increase mortgage-related.
When U.S. घर कीमतें declined steeply after peaking in mid-2006, borrowers ' ability to पुनर्वित्त उनके लोन became अधिक मुश्किल.
As adjustable-rate mortgages began to रीसेट at higher ब्याज rates ( causing उच्चतर monthly भुगतान ), बंधक delinquencies soared.
Securities समर्थित साथ mortgages, सहित subprime mortgages, widely held by वित्तीय firms globally, खोया सबसे of their मान.
वैश्विक investors also drastically reduced purchases of mortgage-backed कर्ज़ और अन्य प्रतिभूति as भाग of a decline in the क्षमता और willingness of the निजी वित्तीय system to support lending.
चिंताएं about the soundness of U.S. credit and वित्तीय बाज़ार led to tightening credit around the संसार and slowing आर्थिक विकास in the u.S. और Europe.
the संकट had कठोर, long-lasting consequences for the u.S. और यूरोपीय economies.
the U.S. डाला a गहन मंदी, साथ nearly 9 लाख jobs lost during 2008 और 2009, roughly 6 % of the workforce.
U.S. आवास prices fell nearly 30 % on औसत and the U.S. भण्डार मार्केट fell approximately 50 % by early 2009.
as of जल्दी 2013, the u.S. भण्डार मार्केट था recovered to इसके pre-crisis peak लकिन आवास कीमतें remained निकट their कम पाइंट और बेरोजगारी remained elevated.
Economic विकास remained below pre-crisis स्तर.
Europe भी continued to struggle साथ its own आर्थिक संकट.
कार्ल जंग in 1910.
Myers और Briggs extrapolated उनके mbti सिद्धान्त इससे जंग 's writings in उसके किताब मनोवैज्ञानिक Types.
The myers-briggs प्रकार indicator ( mbti ) मूल्यांकन is a psychometric questionnaire designed to माप मनोवैज्ञानिक वरीयताओं in how people perceive the संसार और मेक निर्णय.
ये वरीयताओं यहूद extrapolated इससे the typological theories प्रस्तावित by कार्ल गुस्ताव जंग and first published in his 1921 book मनोवैज्ञानिक Types ( English edition, 1923 ).
जंग theorized that वहीँ हैं चार principal psychological functions by जिससे we experience the world : सनसनी, अंतर्ज्ञान, feeling, और सोच.
एक of ये चार कृत्यों is प्रबल सबसे of the समय.
the original developers of the personality inventory were katharine Cook Briggs और उसके daughter, इसाबेल Briggs मायर्स ; ये दो, having studied extensively the कार्य of जंग, turned उनके ब्याज of human बर्ताव into a devotion of turning the theory of psychological types to practical उपयोग.
वे began creating the indicator during World युद्ध II, believing कि a knowledge of personality वरीयताओं होता help महिलाओं जो यहूद प्रवेश the औद्योगिक workforce लिये the first time to पहचानो the sort of war-time कार्य कि होता be `` most comfortable और प्रभावी ''.
the आरंभिक questionnaire grew into the myers-briggs प्रकार Indicator, जिससे थी पहला प्रकाशित in 1962.
the mbti focuses on सामान्य populations and emphasizes the मान of naturally occurring मतभेद.
Robert kaplan और डेनिस Saccuzzo मानना `` the underlying assumption of the mbti is कि we all have विशिष्ट preferences in the रास्ता we construe हमारी अनुभवों, और ये वरीयताओं underlie our रूचि, needs, मान, and प्रेरणा '' ( p. 499 ).
`` यहूदा '' is a सोंग by अमरीकी recording कलाकार महिला गागा, इससे उसके दूसरी स्टुडियो album Born इस Way ( 2011 ).

Written and उत्पादित by Lady गागा and RedOne, `` यहूदा '' is a नृत्य और इलेक्ट्रो house सोंग about a woman in प्रेम साथ a man who betrayed her.
It embodies the incidents कि have haunted गागा in the past, and इसके core meaning refers to the negative भाग of her जीवन that वो ca n't escape.

`` यहूदा '' initially था a दमदार sales खोलने, but थी कम कामयाब commercially in तुलना to गागा 's previous singles.
the सोंग पहुँचे the शीर्ष टेन of the चार्ट in सबसे प्रमुख म्यूज़िक markets, और भी reached the शीर्ष of the charts in South कोरियाई.
a म्यूज़िक वीडियो for the सोंग थी filmed in April 2011, co-directed by गागा और Laurieann Gibson and co-starring Norman reedus.

मारविन gaye ( अप्रैल 2, 1939April 1, 1984 ), born मारविन pentz gay, Jr., was an American singer-songwriter और musician.
gaye helped to आकार the sound of motown रिकॉर्ड in the 1960s with a स्ट्रिंग of हिट्स सहित `` कैसा मीठी It is ( To Be loved by तुम ) `` and `` i सुना it through the grapevine `` और duet रिकार्डिंग साथ Mary कुएं और Tammi Terrell, बाद कमाई the शीर्षक `` Prince of motown '' and `` Prince of आत्मा ''.
दौरान the 1970s, gaye recorded the अवधारणा एल्बम कया 's going on and let 's Get it on and became among the पहला कलाकारों in Motown to break दूर इससे the reins of इसके production कम्पनी.
Gaye 's बाद रिकार्डिंग बहकावे अनेक r & b subgenres such as शांत तूफ़ान and neo-soul.
Following a काल in Europe अंतर्गत a कर निर्वासन in the जल्दी 1980s, Gaye released the 1982 ग्रैमी Award-winning hit `` यौन healing `` और the Midnight प्रेम एल्बम.
Since his death in 1984, gaye has महरूम मरणोपरांत honored by अनेक संस्थानों, including the ग्रैमी Lifetime उपलब्धि पुरस्कार और the Rock and फेंकें Hall of Fame.
the Academy Award for Best Picture is एक of the अकादमी पुरस्कार of मेरिट प्रस्तुत annually by the अकादमी of गति Picture Arts and sciences ( AMPAS ) to निर्माता working in the गति चित्र उद्योग और is the तभी श्रेणी in जिससे every सदस्य is eligible to मनोनीत लिये.

Heavy बरसात is an interactive drama action-adventure वीडियो game निर्मित by French developer quantic सपना exclusively लिये the प्लेस्टेशन 3.

Heavy Rains story is a dramatic thriller modelled after film noir, featuring चार protagonists involved with the रहस्य of the Origami कातिल, a सीरियल कातिल जो उपयोग extended periods of वर्षा to डुबो उसके victims.
ethan मंगल is trying to save उसके son इससे being the अगला शिकार, जबकि investigative journalist मैडिसन Paige, एफबीआई profiler नॉर्मन Jayden, और private detective स्कॉट शेल्बी are प्रत्येक trying to track bas clues to the origami कातिल 's पहचान.
the खिलाड़ी interacts साथ the खेल by performing क्रियाएँ highlighted on स्क्रीन सम्बन्धित to motions on the नियंत्रक, और in कुछ मामले, performing a श्रेणी of जल्दी समय कार्यक्रम during fast-paced action sequences.
The player 's निर्णय और क्रियाएँ दौरान the game होगा affect the narrative.
the प्रमुख characters can be मारे, and निश्चित क्रियाएँ may सीसे to अलग scenes और endings.

Total superannuation उद्योग देनदारी : members निधि and reserves ( A $ लाखो ) चूंकि 1988.
सालाना कुल superannuation उद्योग asset विकास 1996-2005.
Superannuation in Australia refers to the arrangements जिससे लोगों मेक in Australia to have निधि available लिये उन्हें in retirement.
In Australia, superannuation arrangements are government-supported and encouraged, और minimum provisions are अनिवार्य लिये कर्मचारी.
लिये example, employers हैं जरूरी to pay a proportion of an employee 's salaries and मजदूरी ( फिलहाल 9 % ) into a superannuation निधि, लकिन people are encouraged to put aside अतिरिक्त निधि into superannuation.
the minimum obligation required by employers is set to बढ़ाएँ to 12 % gradually stepping annually from 2013 to 2020.
an व्यक्तिगत can withdraw funds आउट of a superannuation fund when the person meets one of the शर्तें of रिलीज contained in अनुसूची 1 of the superannuation उद्योग ( Supervision ) Regulations 1994.

Electoral कॉलेज map प्रर्दशित the results of the 2012 u.S. presidential election.
President बराक ओबामा ( D - il ) जीती the लोकप्रिय vote in 26 states and the ज़िला of Columbia ( denoted in ब्लू ) to capture 332 चुनावी मत.
Former राज्यपाल Mitt romney ( R - ma ) जीती the popular vote in 24 राज्य ( denoted in red ) to कैप्चर 206 चुनावी votes.
cartogram representation of the Electoral College vote लिये the 2012 चुनाव, साथ each वर्गाकार representing एक चुनावी vote.
the United राज्य चुनावी College is the institution that officially elects the President और वाइस अध्यक्ष of the United States प्रत्येक four सालो.
The अध्यक्ष and Vice President हैं नहीं elected सीधे by the voters.
बजाय, they are निर्वाचित by `` निर्वाचक '' जो हैं चुनी by popular vote on a state-by-state आधार.
निर्वाचक हैं apportioned to प्रत्येक राज्य और the District of कोलंबिया, but नहीं to territorial possessions of the United राज्य, ऐसे as Puerto रीको और Guam.
the क्रमांक of निर्वाचक in प्रत्येक राज्य is equal to the क्रमांक of सदस्यों of कॉंग्रेस to जिससे the राज्य is entitled.
the twenty-third Amendment has सदा resulted in the District of कोलंबिया having तीन electors.
वहीँ हैं 538 electors, based on there होने 435 प्रतिनिधि and 100 senators, plus the तीन electors इससे the ज़िला of कोलंबिया.
Electors are pledged to particular presidential और vice presidential candidates, though unpledged electors हैं संभावित.
in सब राज्य, मगर maine और Nebraska, निर्वाचक हैं elected on a `` winner-take-all '' basis.
कि is, सब निर्वाचक pledged to the अध्यक्षीय candidate जो विन्स the सबसे मत in a राज्य become निर्वाचक लिये कि state.
maine and नेब्रास्का उपयोग the `` congressional ज़िला method '', selecting एक elector भीतर each congressional ज़िला by popular vote and selecting the बाकी two electors by a राज्यव्यापी लोकप्रिय vote.
Although no elector is required by federal law to honor a pledge, वहीँ have only महरूम बहुत few अवसरों when an elector voted contrary to a प्रतिज्ञा.
the बारहवीं amendment specifies कैसा a President and Vice अध्यक्ष हैं निर्वाचित और requires प्रत्येक elector to डाल one vote for President और another vote लिये वाइस अध्यक्ष.
Critics argue that the Electoral College is inherently undemocratic और देता झूले राज्य अनुपातहीन influence in electing the President and Vice President.
The चुनावी College gives a न्यूमेरिक लाभ in the चुनाव of the president to the छोटी राज्य, as the न्यूनतम क्रमांक of electors लिये the छोटी states is तीन compared to one लिये the election of प्रतिनिधि.
on the अन्य हाथ, the winner-take-all method of मतदान favors the larger राज्य.
A क्रमांक of संवैधानिक amendments have been प्रस्तावित seeking to alter the Electoral College or बदलें it with a direct लोकप्रिय vote.
Barack Hussein Obama ii ( ; born अगस्त 4, 1961 ) is the 44th और वर्तमान President of the संयुक्त राज्य, the पहला अफ़्रीकी American to थाम the office.
born in Honolulu, Hawaii, Obama is a ग्रैजुएट of कोलंबिया विश्वविद्यालयों और हार्वर्ड विधि स्कूल, जहाँ he थी अध्यक्ष of the हार्वर्ड विधि पुनर्विलोकन.
he थी a community आयोजक in शिकागो पहले कमाई उसके law degree.
he worked as a सिविल अधिकारों attorney in शिकागो और सिखाया संवैधानिक विधि at the विश्वविद्यालयों of शिकागो विधि स्कूल इससे 1992 to 2004.
he परोसा three शर्तें representing the 13th District in the इलिनोइस सीनेट इससे 1997 to 2004, running unsuccessfully for the संयुक्त राज्य House of प्रतिनिधि in 2000.
in 2004, Obama received national ध्यान दौरान उसके अभियान to represent इलिनोइस in the संयुक्त States सीनेट साथ his विजय in the March Democratic पार्टी primary, his keynote address at the लोकतांत्रिक नेशनल सम्मेलन in July, and उसके election to the Senate in नवम्बर.
he began उसके presidential अभियान in 2007, and in 2008, after a बंद प्राथमिक अभियान against हिलेरी rodham Clinton, he won sufficient delegates in the लोकतांत्रिक पार्टी primaries to प्राप्त the presidential nomination.
he then पराजित Republican nominee जॉन McCain in the सामान्य election, और थी उदघाटन as अध्यक्ष on January 20, 2009.
Nine months later, ओबामा थी नामित the 2009 नोबेल Peace Prize laureate.
He was re-elected president in नवम्बर 2012, defeating रिपब्लिकन nominee mitt Romney, and was sworn in लिये a दूसरी term on January 20, 2013.
जल्दी in उसके first पद in office, ओबामा signed into law आर्थिक stimulus विधान in जवाब to the ग्रेट Recession in the रूप of the American रिकवरी and reinvestment अधिनियम of 2009 और the कर राहत, Unemployment बीमे reauthorization, और जॉब सृष्टि अधिनियम of 2010.
Other प्रमुख घरेलू initiatives in his presidency include the रोगी सुरक्षा and सस्ती Care Act, प्रायः referred to as `` obamacare '' ; the dodd–frank वॉल गली सुधार and Consumer सुरक्षा Act ; the do n't पूछो, do n't बताना repeal Act of 2010 ; the बजट कंट्रोल अधिनियम of 2011 ; और the American Taxpayer राहत Act of 2012.
in May 2012, he became the first बैठे u.S. अध्यक्ष to सरेआम support same-sex विवाह और in 2013 उसके प्रशासन दायर briefs जिससे urged the Supreme अदालत to नियम in favor of same-sex युगल in दो high-profile मामले.
in foreign नीति, ओबामा ended U.S. military involvement in the इराकी युद्ध, increased troop स्तर in Afghanistan, signed the New प्रारंभ बाहें कंट्रोल सन्धि साथ Russia, ordered u.S. सैन्य भागीदारी in Libya, और ordered the सैन्य आपरेशन that resulted in the मौत of Osama बिन Laden.

नमूना view of an इलेक्ट्रॉनिक स्वास्थ्य record based on बिंब
Sample view of an electronic स्वास्थ्य रिकार्ड
an इलेक्ट्रॉनिक health रिकार्ड ( EHR ) is an evolving concept पारिभाषित as a systematic collection of electronic health information about individual मरीजों or populations.
it is a रिकार्ड in digital स्वरूप that is theoretically capable of होने साझा across अलग स्वास्थ्य care जमावट.
in कुछ cases इस sharing can occur by रास्ता of network-connected enterprise-wide information प्रणालियों और अन्य सूचना संजाल or exchanges.
ehrs may शामिल a दायरा of data, सहित जनसांख्यिकी, चिकित्सा इतिहास, दवा और allergies, immunization औकात, laboratory परीक्षण results, radiology बिंब, vital लक्षण, personal stats जैसे age और वज़न, and बिलिंग information.
the Mariner up on the mast in a तूफ़ान.
एक of the wood-engraved illustrations by gustave doré.
The rime of the प्राचीन मेरिनर ( originally the Rime of the ancyent Marinere ) is the longest major कविता by the अंग्रेज़ी poet सैमुएल Taylor कॉलरिज, लिखा in 1797–98 and प्रकाशित in 1798 in the पहला संस्करण of Lyrical Ballads.
Modern editions use a later revised संस्करण printed in 1817 कि featured a gloss.
Along साथ अन्य कविताएं in गीतात्मक Ballads, it थी a signal शिफ़्ट to modern काव्य and the शुरूआत of British Romantic साहित्य.
a प्रॉक्सी auto-config ( PAC ) file defines कैसा web browsers और other user agents can automatically choose the उचित प्रॉक्सी सर्वर ( access विधि ) for fetching a दिए url.
a PAC file contains a जावास्क्रिप्ट function “FindProxyForURL ( url, मेजबान ) ”.
इस function returns a string साथ एक or अधिक अभिगम method विशेषताएँ.
ये विशेषताएँ कारण the user agent to use a particular proxy सर्वर or to कनेक्ट सीधे.
अनेक specifications provide a fall-back जब a प्रॉक्सी fails to respond.
The browser fetches इस pac file पहले requesting अन्य यूआरएल.
the URL of the PAC file is either configured manually or determined automatically by the वेब प्रॉक्सी autodiscovery Protocol.

it contains all public-use और military एयरपोर्ट in the राज्य.

आईओएस ( previously iphone os ) is a mobile ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली विकसित and वितरित by ठहराना Inc. originally released in 2007 लिये the iphone और iPod टच प्लेटफ़ॉर्म, it रै been extended to support other ठहराना डिवाइस such as the ipad और Apple tv.
नापसंद microsoft 's खिड़कियाँ Phone और google 's एंड्रॉइड, ठहराना करता नहीं अनुज्ञा आईओएस for installation on non-apple हार्डवेयर.
, ठहराना 's app स्टोर contained अधिक than 700,000 iOS अनुप्रयोग, जिससे have collectively been डाउनलोड more than 30 अरब टाइम्स.
it था a 21 % share of the smartphone मोबाईल ऑपरेटिंग system इकाई shipped in the चौथी क्वार्टर of 2012, पीछे only google 's Android.
in जून 2012, it accounted लिये 65 % of mobile वेब आंकड़ा खपत ( सहित use on दोनो the ipod टच and the iPad ).
At the हाफ of 2012, there यहूद 410 लाख डिवाइस activated.
According to the special मीडिया इवेंट आयोजित by ठहराना on September 12, 2012, 400 लाख devices have been sold through June 2012.
The उपयोक्ता इंटरफ़ेस of iOS is आधारित on the अवधारणा of सीधा हेरफेर, using multi-touch gestures.
इंटरफ़ेस control elements consist of sliders, switches, और बटन.
बातचीत साथ the os includes gestures ऐसे as swipe, tap, पिंच, और रिवर्स pinch, all of जिससे have specific परिभाषाएं भीतर the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of the iOS operating प्रणाली and इसके multi-touch इंटरफ़ेस.
आतंरिक accelerometers are प्रयुक्त by कुछ applications to respond to shaking the device ( एक आम result is the undo command ) or rotating it in तीन आयाम ( एक आम result is switching इससे portrait to लैंडस्केप mode ).
iOS is derived from OS x, साथ जिससे it साझा the Darwin न्यास.
आईओएस is Apple 's मोबाईल संस्करण of the os x ऑपरेटिंग system used on Apple कंप्यूटर.
in आईओएस, वहीँ हैं four abstraction layers : the कोर os परत, the Core Services परत, the मीडिया परत, और the Cocoa टच layer.
The current version of the ऑपरेटिंग system ( आईओएस 6.1.3 ) dedicates 1-1.5 gb of the यंत्र 's फ्लैश मेमोरी for the प्रणाली विभाजन, using roughly 800 MB of that partition ( varying by मॉडल ) लिये आईओएस itself.
आईओएस currently runs on iPhone, ipad, iPod touch and Apple TV.

a बिगाड़ने is an automotive aerodynamic device whose intended design function is to 'spoil ' unfavorable air गति across a देह of a vehicle in motion, प्रायः वर्णित as turbulence or खीचें.
विघ्न on the सामने of a vehicle हैं often पुकारा air dams, क्युकी in addition to directing एयर प्रवाह वे also reduce the amount of air बहती underneath the गाडी which generally reduces aerodynamic लिफ्ट and खीचें.
Spoilers are प्रायः fitted to रेस और high-performance sports गाड़ियाँ, हालांकि they have become common on यात्री vehicles as खूब.
कुछ spoilers हैं added to cars primarily लिये styling उद्देश्य and have either छोटी aerodynamic benefit or even मेक the aerodynamics worse.
Spoilers लिये गाड़ियाँ are प्रायः incorrectly उलझन साथ, or the पद used interchangeably साथ, wings.
ऑटोमोटिव विंग्स are डिवाइस whose intended design is to generate downforce as air गुजरता around उन्हें, not simply disrupt existing airflow पैटर्न.

इस is a list of video खेल जहाँ the character मारियो plays a भाग, either as the protagonist, antagonist, supporting character, as भाग of an ensemble cast, as a कैमियो, or in a game within a game.
It does नहीं शामिल सरल सन्दर्भ to the अक्षर, such as the portraits of Mario मिला in the लेजेंड of Zelda : a Link to the पास्ट.
The साल indicated is the साल the game थी पहला released, सबसे commonly in Japan ; games यहूद sometimes released years बाद in other regions of the world.
The सूची includes ports, remakes और compilations.
it करता n't शामिल any Virtual कंसोल re-releases.
`` Man of निरंतर Sorrow '' ( भी ज्ञात as `` i Am A man of Constant विषाद '' ) is a परंपरागत अमरीकी folk सोंग पहला अंकित by लंड burnett, a partially अँधा fiddler from केंटकी.
the song was originally अंकित by Burnett as `` विदाई सोंग '' मुद्रित in a रिचर्ड burnett songbook, circa 1913.
an early version थी recorded by emry आर्थर in 1928 ( vocalion Vo 5208 ).
Public ब्याज in the सोंग थी renewed after the रिलीज of the 2000 film o bhai, जहाँ Art Thou ?
, as it plays a central role in the फिल्मी 's प्लाट.

जोसेफसन जंक्शन array चिप developed by the नेशनल ब्यूरो of Standards as a standard volt
the volt ( प्रतीक : v ) is the SI निकला ईकाई for इलेक्ट्रिक संभावित ( वोल्टेज ), इलेक्ट्रिक संभावित अंतर, और electromotive फ़ोर्स.
the volt is named in सम्मान of the इतालवी physicist alessandro Volta ( 1745–1827 ), who invented the वोल्टायिक pile, संभवतः the पहला chemical बैटरी.
a प्लैक commemorating the location of the साराजेवो हत्या और कदम of gavrilo princip ( image लिया in 1987, पहले कदम were removed in 1992 and plaque बदला इससे cyrillic to Latin स्क्रिप्ट )
a plaque commemorating the location of the साराजेवो assassination ( image taken in 2009 )
on 28 June 1914, archduke फ्रांज Ferdinand of ऑस्ट्रिया, heir presumptive to the Austro-Hungarian सिंहासन, और उसके बीवी, सोफी, duchess of hohenberg, were शॉट dead in साराजेवो, by gavrilo princip, one of a group of छह Bosnian Serb assassins coordinated by Danilo ilić.
the राजनैतिक objective of the assassination थी to break बंद austria-hungary 's south-slav provinces so वे could be संयुक्त into a Greater सर्बिया or a यूगोस्लाविया.
the assassins ' motives यहूद consistent साथ the गति कि बाद became ज्ञात as Young बोस्निया.
Serbian सैन्य अधिकारियों stood पीछे the attack.
at the शीर्ष of ये सर्बियाई military conspirators was मुख्य of Serbian Military प्रज्ञा Dragutin dimitrijević, उसके righthand man Major Vojislav tankosić, और masterspy Rade malobabić.
प्रमुख tankosić armed the assassins साथ बम और pistols और प्रशिक्षित उन्हें.
The हत्यारे यहूद given अभिगम to the same clandestine टनल of safe-houses and एजेंटों कि Rade malobabić used लिये the घुसपैठ of weapons and operatives into Austria-Hungary.
the assassins, the key सदस्यों of the clandestine टनल, and the key सर्बियाई सैन्य conspirators जो यहूद still जिंदा were arrested, आजमाया, convicted and punished.
those who were गिरफ्तार in बोस्निया यहूद tried in साराजेवो in October 1914.
The अन्य conspirators यहूद arrested और आजमाया पहले a सर्बियाई कंगारू अदालत on the french-controlled Salonika Front in 1916–1917 on unrelated false आरोप ; Serbia executed तीन of the शीर्ष सैन्य षड्यंत्रकारियों.
much of कया is ज्ञात परिचय the assassinations comes from these दो ट्रायल and related records.
कार्यभार of जिम्मेदारी लिये the bombing and हत्याएं of 28 जून is अत्यधिक विवादास्पद because the आक्रमण led to the outbreak of संसार युद्ध i एक month बाद.
मिशन San जुआन capistrano थी a Spanish मिशन in Southern कैलिफ़ोर्निया, स्तिथ in present-day सैन जुआन Capistrano.
it was founded on सब Saints ' दिन नवम्बर 1, 1776, by Spanish catholics of the franciscan अनुक्रम.
Named for Giovanni da capistrano, a 15th century theologian and `` योद्धा पुजारी '' जो resided in the abruzzo region of Italy, San जुआन capistrano has the भेद of होने home to the oldest building in California still in use, a chapel built in 1782.
Known alternately as `` Serra 's चैपल '' and `` पिता Serra 's गिरिजाघर, '' it is the only extant ढांचा where it has महरूम प्रलेखित कि the padre junipero सेरा celebrated द्रव्यमान.
एक of the बेहतरीन ज्ञात of the Alta California missions ( and एक of the few मिशन to have दरअसल महरूम संस्थापित twice—others होने मिशन सैन Gabriel arcángel और मिशन la purísima concepción ).
the साईट थी originally consecrated on October 30, 1775, by पिता fermín lasuén, लकिन was जल्दी abandoned due to अशांति among the स्वदेशी population in सैन डिएगो.
the success of the उपनिवेश is evident in its historical records.
prior to the आगमन of the missionaries, कुछ 550 natives यहूद बिखरे throughout the local area.
by 1790, the क्रमांक of परिवर्तित Christians had grown to 700, and बस छह सालो बाद nearly 1,000 `` neophytes `` ( recent converts ) lived in or around the Mission यौगिक.
1,649 baptisms were conducted कि year alone, आउट of the कुल 4,639 souls परिवर्तित between 1776 और 1847.
अधिक than 2,000 पूर्व निवासियों ( ज़्यादातर juaneño Indians ) are दफ्न in unmarked क़ब्रों in the मिशन 's कब्रिस्तान ( campo सेंटो ).
The remains of Father ( बाद monsignor ) st. John o'sullivan, who पहचाना the property 's ऐतिहासिक मान और working tirelessly to conserve और rebuild its structures, are दफ्न at the entrance to the cemetery on the west side of the property, and a प्रतिमा उठाया in उसके honor stands at the सिर of the क्रिप्ट.
The surviving chapel भी serves as the final resting प्लेस of तीन padres who passed on while सेवारत at the मिशन : Fathers जोस Barona, Vicente Fustér, और Vicente पास्कुआल oliva are सब entombed beneath the अभयारण्य floor.
the criolla or `` Mission grape, '' was first planted at San जुआन Capistrano in 1779 ; in 1783, the पहला वाइन उत्पादित in alta कैलिफ़ोर्निया emerged from the मिशन 's वाइनरी.
The Mission डाला a long काल of क्रमिक मनाही बाद secularization in 1833.
numerous प्रयत्न यहूद बना over the सालो to restore the Mission to its पूर्व glory, but none met with ग्रेट कामयाबी until the arrival of पिता O'Sullivan in 1910.
बहाली प्रयत्न continue, और `` Serra 's चैपल '' is स्टिल प्रयुक्त लिये धार्मिक सेवाएं.
About half-a-million visitors, सहित 80,000 school children, आइये to the मिशन प्रत्येक साल.
और जबकि the ruins of `` the ग्रेट स्टोन गिरिजाघर '' ( जिससे थी all लकिन leveled by an 1812 भूकंप ) हैं a renowned architectural अचरज, the Mission is शायद best ज्ञात for the सालाना `` वापसी of the Swallows '' which is traditionally observed every March 19 ( संत जोसेफ 's दिन ).
मिशन San जुआन capistrano has served as a पसंदीदा subject लिये अनेक notable artists, और has been immortalized in साहित्य and on फिल्मी numerous टाइम्स, शायद अधिक than कोई अन्य मिशन.
in 1984, a आधुनिक गिरिजाघर जटिल was constructed बस उत्तर और west of the मिशन compound and is now ज्ञात as मिशन Basilica सैन जुआन capistrano.
Today, the मिशन यौगिक serves as a संग्रहालय, with the सेरा Chapel within the यौगिक serving as a चैपल for the मिशन parish.

Mercedes-Benz superdome ( originally louisiana superdome and commonly the Superdome ) is a खेल और प्रदर्शनी स्टेडियम, located in the सेंट्रल कारोबार ज़िला of New ऑरलियन्स, Louisiana, यूएसए.
Plans were drawn up in 1967, by the नई Orleans modernist architectural firm of Curtis और Davis.
इसके steel फ़्रेम covers a expanse.
इसके गुम्बद is बना of a Lamella multi-ringed frame and has a व्यास of, बनाना it the largest फिक्स्ड domed ढांचा in the संसार.
it is घर to the एनएफएल 's नई ऑरलियन्स संतो, the ncaa 's Division I-A tulane Green Wave फ़ुटबॉल टोली ( the largest फ़ुटबॉल स्टेडियम in सम्मेलन यूएसए ), the राज्य फार्म Bayou क्लासिक, the R+L वाहक नई Orleans Bowl, the allstate Sugar कटोरी and, प्रत्येक fourth साल, the bcs नेशनल Championship खेल.
क्युकी of the size और स्थान in one of the प्रमुख tourist गंतव्यों in the United राज्य, the superdome routinely makes the `` छोटी list '' of candidates being माना लिये major sporting कार्यक्रम, ऐसे as the सुपर कटोरी और the Final चार.
In 2005, the Superdome gained अंतरराष्ट्रीय ध्यान of a अलग type जब it housed thousands of लोगों seeking shelter from Hurricane Katrina.
The भवन suffered extensive क्षति as a परिणाम of the तूफ़ान, and थी बंद लिये many महीने afterward.

it खोली on April 16, 2001.

डिज़्नी 's Animal किंगडम आवास is स्तिथ in the एनिमल Kingdom रिज़ॉर्ट क्षेत्रफल, सटा to डिज़्नी 's एनिमल Kingdom.
It gives अतिथि the अवसर to view चरने वन्यजीव बाहर their rooms and public क्षेत्रों in the रिज़ॉर्ट within निकटता of the animals, conveying the अहसास of being in an African सवाना.
The लोगों 's Party, also ज्ञात as the `` populists '', was a short-lived राजनैतिक पार्टी in the संयुक्त States स्थापित in 1891 during the populist गति ( United States, 19th सदी ).
it was most महत्वपूर्ण in 1892-96, and तब rapidly faded away.
आधारित among poor, श्वेत कपास farmers in the दक्षिण ( विशेषकर उत्तर कैरोलिना, Alabama, और Texas ) और hard-pressed wheat किसानो in the plains states ( especially Kansas and नेब्रास्का ), it represented a कट्टरपंथी crusading form of agrarianism और दुश्मनी to banks, railroads, and elites generally.
it sometimes formed coalitions with मजदूर unions, और in 1896 the डेमोक्रेट endorsed उनके presidential nominee, William जेनिंग्स ब्रायन.
the terms `` populist '' and `` populism `` हैं commonly used लिये anti-elitist appeals in विपक्ष to स्थापित रूचि and mainstream parties.

There हैं hundreds of languages बोला in सीरियल.
the प्रमुख भाषाएं are योरूबा, हौसा, Igbo, Edo, fulfulde, कनूरी, and ibb.
The official भाषा of Nigeria, अंग्रेज़ी, the पूर्व colonial भाषा, थी chosen to facilitate the सांस्कृतिक and linguistic एकता of the country.
अंग्रेज़ी, however, remains an exclusive preserve of the देश 's urban elite, and is नहीं widely spoken in ग्रामीण क्षेत्रों, which comprise तीन quarters of the देशों जनसांख्यिकी.
सीरियल 's linguistic diversity is a microcosm of Africa as a पूरे, encompassing तीन major African languages families : afroasiatic, Nilo-Saharan, and niger–congo.
सीरियल also रै several as-yet unclassified languages, such as cen tuum, जिससे may represent a relic of an even greater diversity prior to the spread of the वर्तमान language परिवारों.
A series of events led to the आक्रमण on पर्ल हार्बर.
War between Japan और the संयुक्त States had been a सम्भावना that each nation 's सैन्य शक्तियां नियोजित लिये since the 1920s, हालांकि रियल tension did नहीं begin जबतक the 1931 invasion of मंचूरिया by Japan.
Over the next दशक, जापानी विस्तारित धीरे into चीन, leading to सब आउट युद्ध between the दो in 1937.
in 1940 जापानी invaded French Indochina in an प्रयत्न to embargo all imports into चीन, सहित युद्ध आपूर्तियाँ खरीदा इससे the U.S.
इस move prompted the United राज्य to embargo सब oil निर्यात, अग्रणी the इम्पीरियल जापानी Navy to अनुमान that it था कम than दो years of bunker oil बाकी and to support the मौजूदा plans to seize आयल संसाधन in the डच East इंडीज.
नियोजन had been underway लिये कुछ समय on an attack on the `` दक्षिणी संसाधन Area '' to add it to the वृहद ईस्ट एशिया co-prosperity गोला कि जापानी envisioned in the Pacific.
The फिलीपीन islands, at कि समय an अमरीकी territory, यहूद also a जापानी target.
the जापानी military concluded that an invasion of the फिलीपीन होता provoke an अमरीकी सैन्य जवाब.
Rather than seize and fortify the आइलैंड्स, and इंतजार लिये the inevitable us counterattack, जापानी 's military नेताओ instead decided on the pre-emptive Pearl Harbor attack, which they assumed होता negate the अमरीकी शक्तियां needed for the मुक्ति और reconquest of the आइलैंड्स.
नियोजन लिये the attack था begun in बहुत early 1941, by Admiral Isoroku यामामोटो.
He आखिरकार won assent from the नवल ऊँची Command by, among अन्य बाते, threatening to इस्तीफा.
The attack थी approved in the गर्मियाँ at an इम्पीरियल सम्मेलन और again at a दूसरी सम्मेलन in the पतन.
Simultaneously over the साल, pilots यहूद प्रशिक्षित, और ships prepared लिये इसके निष्पादन.
प्राधिकार for the आक्रमण was granted at the second Imperial सम्मेलन if a राजनयिक result satisfactory to Japan was नहीं पहुँचे.
बाद फाइनल स्वीकृति by सम्राट हिरोहितो the order to आक्रमण थी जारी at the शुरूआत of दिसम्बर.
A आम दफ्तर stapler
A आम स्कूल stapler
A stapler is a mechanical यंत्र that joins sheets of paper or समान सामग्री by ड्राइविंग a thin metal स्टेपल through the चादरें and folding the ends.
Staplers are widely प्रयुक्त in government, business, कार्यालयों, घरों and स्कूलों.
the word `` stapler '' can actually refer to a क्रमांक of अलग devices of varying uses.
in addition to joining पेपर sheets together, staplers can भी be प्रयुक्त in a सर्जिकल सेटिंग to जुड़ें ऊतक together with सर्जिकल staples to बंद a सर्जिकल घाव ( much in the वही रास्ता as टांके or sutures ).
typically, सबसे staplers हैं used to जुड़ें अनेक sheets of पेपर.
पेपर staplers आइये in दो distinct types : manual और इलेक्ट्रिक.
हस्तचालित staplers are सामान्यतः hand-held, although मॉडल that हैं used जबकि set on a डेस्क or अन्य सतह हैं नहीं uncommon.
Electric staplers मौजूद in a किस्में of अलग डिजाइन and models.
उनके प्राथमिक ऑपरेटिंग फलन is to जुड़ें विशाल numbers of पेपर चादरें साथ in रैपिड उत्तराधिकार.
कुछ इलेक्ट्रिक staplers can join up to 20 चादरें at a समय.
swallowing, ज्ञात scientifically as deglutition, is the प्रक्रम in the इंसान or animal देह कि makes something pass from the मुँह, to the pharynx, और into the esophagus, जबकि shutting the epiglottis.
if this fails और the ऑब्जेक्ट goes through the trachea, तब choking or pulmonary aspiration can occur.
In the इंसान देह it is नियंत्रित by the swallowing reflex.
thaddeus स्टीवंस ( अप्रैल 4, 1792 – August 11, 1868 ), of पेन्सिलवेनिया, थी a leader of the Radical रिपब्लिकन faction of the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी और a fierce opponent of गुलामी.
he was एक of the most influential सदस्यों in the इतिहास of कॉंग्रेस.
as chairman of the powerful House Ways और अर्थात् कमेटी, स्टीवंस, a witty, व्यंग्यात्मक speaker and flamboyant party leader, वर्चस्व the House इससे 1861 जबतक उसके मौत.
He लिखा much of the वित्तीय विधान that सशुल्क लिये the अमरीकी Civil युद्ध.
Stevens and Senator चार्ल्स sumner यहूद the prime नेताओ of the Radical republicans दौरान the war and पुनर्निर्माण era.
scholarly दृश्य of Stevens have swung sharply चूंकि उसके मौत as interpretations of पुनर्निर्माण have changed.
इतिहासकारों of the dunning स्कूल ( 1890s–1940s ) आयोजित Stevens जिम्मेदार लिये demanding हर्ष उपचार of the white दक्षिण और violating American परंपराओं of republicanism, depicting Stevens as a villain लिये his वकालत of हर्ष measures in the South ऐसे as disfranchising all ex-Confederates.
इस अत्यधिक ऋणात्मक characterization आयोजित sway into the 1950s.
the rise of the neo-abolitionist school in the 1950s led to a strong धनात्मक सराहना of स्टीवंस ' कार्य on सिविल अधिकारों for Freedmen.
a recent biographer characterizes उसे as, `` the Great commoner, savior of free पब्लिक education in Pennsylvania, नेशनल रिपब्लिकन नेता in the struggles against slavery in the संयुक्त राज्य and intrepid mainstay of the attempt to secure racial इंसाफ for the freedmen दौरान Reconstruction, the तभी सदस्य of the हाउस of Representatives कभी to have been known as the 'dictator ' of कॉंग्रेस. ''
अवलोकन of the translation of eukaryotic मेसेंजर RNA
Diagram प्रर्दशित the अनुवाद of mrna and the संश्लेषण of प्रोटीन by a राइबोसोम
in आणविक जीवविज्ञान and आनुवंशिकी, अनुवाद is the प्रक्रम through which cellular ribosomes manufacture प्रोटीन.
it is part of the प्रक्रम of जीन expression.
In अनुवाद, messenger rna ( mrna ) produced by ट्रांसक्रिप्शन is decoded by the राइबोसोम to उपज a specific amino acid chain, or polypeptide, that होगा later fold into an क्रियाशील प्रोटीन.
In bacteria, अनुवाद occurs in the cell 's कोशिकाद्रव्य, जहाँ the large and छोटी subunits of the राइबोसोम हैं located, और bind to the mrna.
in eukaryotes, अनुवाद occurs across the membrane of the endoplasmic reticulum in a प्रक्रम पुकारा vectorial संश्लेषण.
the ribosome facilitates डिकोडिंग by inducing the binding of tRNAs with complementary anticodon sequences to कि of the mRNA.
The tRNAs carry विशिष्ट अमीनो acids कि are chained साथ into a polypeptide as the mrna गुजरता through and is `` पढ़ा '' by the राइबोसोम in a फ़ैशन reminiscent to that of a stock टिकर और टिकर टेप.
in अनेक उदाहरण, the संपूर्ण ribosome/mrna जटिल बांधता to the बाहरी झिल्ली of the अशिष्ट endoplasmic reticulum और रिलीज the nascent प्रोटीन polypeptide inside लिये later vesicle transport and secretion outside of the कोशिका.
Many types of transcribed rna, ऐसे as transfer rna, ribosomal RNA, और छोटी nuclear rna, do नहीं undergo अनुवाद into प्रोटीन.
Translation proceeds in चार phases : दीक्षा, elongation, translocation and termination ( all describing the growth of the अमीनो acid chain, or polypeptide कि is the product of अनुवाद ).
Amino acids are brought to ribosomes और समवेत into प्रोटीन.
in सक्रियण, the सही amino एसिड is covalently bonded to the सही transfer rna ( tRNA ).
the अमीनो एसिड is joined by इसके carboxyl group to the 3 ' OH of the trna by an ester बंध.
When the trna has an amino acid linked to it, it is termed `` चार्ज ''.
दीक्षा involves the small subunit of the ribosome binding to the 5 ' समाप्त of mrna साथ the help of दीक्षा कारकों ( if ).
termination of the polypeptide happens when the A site of the राइबोसोम faces a रोकें codon ( UAA, uag, or uga ).
no trna can recognize or bind to this codon.
Instead, the रोकें codon induces the binding of a release factor protein that prompts the disassembly of the संपूर्ण ribosome/mrna जटिल.
a क्रमांक of एंटीबायोटिक अधिनियम by inhibiting translation ; these include anisomycin, cycloheximide, chloramphenicol, tetracycline, streptomycin, erythromycin, and puromycin, among अन्य.
Prokaryotic ribosomes have a अलग structure इससे that of eukaryotic ribosomes, और यूँ एंटीबायोटिक can specifically निशाना बैक्टीरियल infections without any detriment to a eukaryotic host 's cells.
a multimedia संदेश on a मोबाईल फोन.
मल्टीमीडिया messaging सेवा ( MMS ) is a मानक रास्ता to भेजें संदेश that शामिल मल्टीमीडिया सामग्री to and from mobile फोन.
it extends the core sms ( छोटी संदेश सेवा ) capability that अनुमत एक्सचेंज of टेक्स्ट संदेश only up to 160 वर्ण in लंबाई.
the सबसे popular उपयोग is to भेजें photographs इससे camera-equipped handsets, although it is भी लोकप्रिय as a method of delivering न्यूज और entertainment content सहित videos, pictures, text पृष्ठों और ringtones.
The मानक is developed by the खोलें Mobile Alliance ( ओमो ), although दौरान विकास it was part of the 3gpp और वैप समूह.
smallpox थी an संक्रामक disease अद्वितीय to इंसानो, caused by either of दो वायरस variants, variola major and variola नाबालिग.
The बीमारी is भी ज्ञात by the लैटिन names variola or variola वीरा, निकला इससे varius ( `` spotted '' ) or varus ( `` मुंहासे '' ).
The बीमारी was originally ज्ञात in English as the `` pox '' or `` red प्लेग '' ; the पद `` smallpox '' was पहला प्रयुक्त in Britain in the 15th century to फर्क variola from the `` ग्रेट pox '' ( उपदंश ).
the पिछला naturally occurring case of smallpox ( variola minor ) थी diagnosed on 26 October 1977.
smallpox localized in छोटी रक्त बरतन of the स्किन and in the mouth और गला.
in the स्किन it resulted in a characteristic maculopapular खाज and, बाद, उठाया fluid-filled फफोले.
V. प्रमुख produces a अधिक serious disease और रै an overall mortality rate of 30–35 %.
V. minor causes a milder रूप of बीमारी ( भी known as alastrim, cottonpox, milkpox, whitepox, और Cuban खुजली ) which मारता परिचय 1 % of इसके victims.
long-term complications of V. प्रमुख संक्रमण शामिल characteristic scars, commonly on the फेस, जिससे occur in 65–85 % of survivors.
दृष्टिहीनता resulting from corneal ulceration and scarring, और limb deformities due to गठिया and osteomyelitis are कम आम जटिलताओं, देखी in परिचय 2–5 % of cases.
Smallpox is believed to have emerged in इंसान populations about 10,000 BC.
the earliest शारीरिक evidence of it is संभवतः the pustular rash on the mummified body of pharaoh Ramses v of Egypt.
the disease मारे an अनुमानित 400,000 Europeans annually दौरान the closing years of the 18th century ( including पाँच reigning monarchs ), और was जिम्मेदार लिये a third of all दृष्टिहीनता.
Of सब those infected, 20–60 % —and over 80 % of infected children—died from the बीमारी.
Smallpox थी responsible लिये an estimated 300–500 million deaths दौरान the 20th सदी.
as recently as 1967, the World स्वास्थ्य संगठन ( जो ) अनुमानित कि 15 million लोगों contracted the बीमारी और कि two million died in कि साल.
बाद टीकाकरण campaigns throughout the 19th और 20th centuries, the जो certified the eradication of smallpox in 1979.
smallpox is एक of two संक्रामक रोगों to have महरूम eradicated, the other होने rinderpest, जिससे was declared eradicated in 2011.
`` I want to थाम Your Hand '' is a song by the अंग्रेज़ी चट्टान बैंड the बीटल्स.
Written by John Lennon और पॉल McCartney, and अंकित in अक्तूबर 1963, it थी the first बीटल्स रिकार्ड to be बना using four-track उपकरण.
With अग्रिम आदेश exceeding एक million copies in the संयुक्त किंगडम, `` i Want to Hold अपना Hand '' होता ordinarily have gone straight to the शीर्ष of the British रिकार्ड चार्ट on its दिन of रिलीज ( 29 November 1963 ) था it नहीं महरूम blocked by the समूह 's पहला लाख विक्रेता `` वो loves तुम ``, the Beatles ' previous uk single, which was having a resurgent spell in the शीर्ष स्थिति following तीव्र मीडिया coverage of the समूह.
लेने दो सप्ताह to dislodge its पूर्ववर्ती, `` I want to Hold Your हाथ '' stayed at क्रमांक एक लिये five weeks और remained in the uk शीर्ष पचास लिये twenty-one सप्ताह in total.
it थी भी the समूह 's पहला अमरीकी क्रमांक one, प्रवेश the Billboard Hot 100 चार्ट on 18 January 1964 at क्रमांक forty-five और starting the British invasion of the American म्यूज़िक industry.
by 1 फ़रवरी it आयोजित the number एक spot — for सात सप्ताह — पहले होने replaced by `` वो loves You '', a reverse परिदृश्य of कया had occurred in Britain, और remained in the us चार्ट for a कुल of पंद्रह weeks.
`` I Want to थाम Your Hand '' became the बीटल्स ' best-selling सिंगल विश्वव्यापी.
a gasser थी a प्रकार of hot rod originating on the dragstrips of the संयुक्त States in the late 1950s और continued until the early 1970s.
gassers यहूद आधारित on उत्पादन models इससे the 1930s to mid-1960s, which have महरूम stripped of extraneous वज़न और jacked up using a truck बीम धुरी to provide बेहतर weight वितरण on त्वरण ( बीम axles are also lighter than an independent सामने बर्खास्तगी ), हालांकि a raised भण्डार front बर्खास्तगी is आम as well.
आम वज़न कटौती techniques शामिल fiberglass देह panels, stripped इंटीरियर्स और plexiglass खिड़कियाँ ( sometimes रंग tinted ).
क्युकी वे were primarily निर्मित for रेसिंग, ये cars typically था the इंजन swapped to a larger or more शक्तिशाली one, the मौजूदा stock engine modified ( often heavily ) or both.
it was बहुत आम to fit a Roots supercharger और mechanical ईंधन इंजेक्शन, such as एक from algon, hilborn, or crower.
With form being लिखवाई by function, their appearance is प्रायः very top heavy and ungainly, largely due to front ends being उठाया higher than भण्डार, to assist in the weight ट्रांसफ़र दौरान रैपिड acceleration ( रेसिंग ).
having their exhaust pipes निकास through the front फेंडर खूब is a आम characteristic of gassers, as is having लाशें चित्रित in flamboyant metalflakes, मोती, and candy finishes complemented by lettering in wild फ़ॉन्ट्स.
the नाम arose because वे competed in a gasoline -fueled खीचें रेसिंग class, rather than एक using methanol or nitromethane.
The gasser is the पूर्ववर्ती of the modern मजेदार car.
twelve-lead EKG of a 26-year-old male
electrocardiography ( ECG or EKG from ) is a transthoracic ( आरपार the वक्ष or छाती ) निर्वचन of the विद्युत activity of the दिल over a काल of समय, as detected by electrodes attached to the सतह of the स्किन और recorded by a यंत्र बाह्य to the देह.
the रिकॉर्डिंग produced by इस noninvasive procedure is termed an electrocardiogram ( भी ईसीजी or ईकेजी ).
An ECG is प्रयुक्त to माप the rate and नियमितता of heartbeats, as खूब as the size और स्थिति of the कक्षों, the उपस्थिति of कोई क्षति to the heart, and the प्रभाव of दवाएँ or डिवाइस used to विनियमित the दिल, ऐसे as a pacemaker.
सबसे ECGs हैं performed for diagnostic or शोध purposes on इंसान दिल, लकिन may भी be performed on animals, प्रायः लिये diagnosis of heart abnormalities or शोध.
डोनाल्ड John ट्रम्प, Sr. ( born जून 14, 1946 ) is an अमरीकी business महारथी, टेलीविज़न व्यक्तित्व और author.
he is the अध्यक्ष और president of the ट्रम्प संगठन and the founder of Trump Entertainment रिसॉर्ट.
Trump 's extravagant lifestyle, outspoken manner, and role on the एनबीसी वास्तविकता दिखाएँ the प्रशिक्षु have बना him a well-known हस्ती who थी no. 14 on the 2012 Forbes Celebrity 100 list.
Trump is the बेटे of Fred Trump, a धनवान New यॉर्क नगर real-estate developer.
he worked for his father 's firm, Elizabeth ट्रम्प & बेटे, while attending the Wharton School of the University of पेन्सिलवेनिया, और in 1968 officially joined the company.

`` A Change Is Gon na Come '' is a 1964 सिंगल by r & B singer-songwriter sam cooke, लिखा और first recorded in 1963 and released under the आरसीए विक्टर label shortly after his death in late 1964.

भाप उठती इससे the nesjavellir Geothermal शक्ति स्टेशन in आइसलैंड.
geothermal उर्जा is thermal उर्जा उत्पन्न और stored in the धरती.
Thermal उर्जा is the उर्जा कि determines the तापमान of matter.
The geothermal उर्जा of the Earth 's क्रस्ट originates इससे the असली formation of the planet ( 20 % ) और इससे रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय of minerals ( 80 % ).
The geothermal gradient, which is the अंतर in तापमान between the core of the planet और its सतह, ड्राइव a continuous conduction of thermal उर्जा in the form of ऊष्मा from the कोर to the surface.
the क्रियाशील geothermal originates from the यूनानी जड़ें γη ( ge ), meaning earth, और θερμος ( thermos ), meaning hot.
at the core of the Earth, थर्मल उर्जा is created by radioactive decay और temperatures may पहुँचें over 5000 °c ( 9,000 °F ).
ऊष्मा conducts इससे the कोर to surrounding cooler rock.
the high तापमान और pressure कारण कुछ rock to melt, बनाना magma संवहन upward since it is हल्का than the solid rock.
the magma heats rock and जल in the क्रस्ट, sometimes up to 370 °c ( 700 °f ).
इससे hot स्रोतों, geothermal उर्जा has महरूम प्रयुक्त लिये स्नान चूंकि Paleolithic times and लिये space हीटिंग since प्राचीन रोमन times, लकिन it is now बेहतर known लिये विद्युत generation.
Worldwide, about 10,715 megawatts ( mw ) of geothermal power is ऑनलाइन in 24 देशों.
an अतिरिक्त 28 gigawatts of सीधा geothermal heating क्षमता is installed लिये district हीटिंग, स्पेस हीटिंग, spas, औद्योगिक processes, desalination और agricultural applications.
Geothermal शक्ति is लागत प्रभावी, विश्वसनीय, sustainable, और environmentally दोस्ताना, लकिन रै historically been सीमित to areas निकट tectonic थाली सीमाएँ.
Recent technological advances have dramatically expanded the दायरा and आकार of सुगठित संसाधन, विशेषकर for applications such as home हीटिंग, opening a संभावित लिये widespread शोषण.
geothermal wells रिलीज ग्रीनहाउस gases trapped deep भीतर the earth, but ये emissions are much निम्नतर प्रति उर्जा ईकाई than those of fossil fuels.
as a परिणाम, geothermal शक्ति has the potential to सहायता mitigate वैश्विक वार्मिंग if widely तैनात in प्लेस of चट्टान fuels.
the धरती 's geothermal संसाधन are theoretically अधिक than पर्याप्त to सप्लाई मानवता 's energy needs, लकिन तभी a बहुत small भिन्न may be profitably exploited.
खुदाई और exploration लिये गहन resources is very महंगी.
forecasts लिये the future of geothermal शक्ति निर्भर on assumptions about technology, उर्जा prices, subsidies, और interest rates.
Pilot कार्यक्रम like EWEB 's ग्राहक opt in ग्रीन Power Program show कि ग्राहक would be willing to pay a little अधिक लिये a renewable उर्जा सोर्स like geothermal.
But as a result of सरकारी assisted research and उद्योग अनुभव, the cost of generating geothermal शक्ति has decreased by 25 % over the पास्ट दो decades.
In 2001, geothermal उर्जा लागत between दो और ten cents प्रति सम्पात.
Ownership of प्रॉपर्टी may be निजी, सामूहिक, or common and the प्रॉपर्टी may be वस्तुएँ, land/real एस्टेट, or intellectual property.
determining ownership in विधि involves determining who रै निश्चित अधिकारों and duties over the property.
These अधिकारों और duties, sometimes पुकारा a 'bundle of rights ', can be separated और held by different parties.
The सवाल of स्वामित्व पहुँच वापस to the प्राचीन philosophers, प्लेटो and अरस्तू, जो held अलग राय on the subject.
प्लेटो ( 428/427 BC – 348/347 BC ) thought private property created divisive inequalities, while अरस्तू ( 384 bc – 322 bc ) विचार निजी प्रॉपर्टी enabled लोगों to प्राप्त the पूरा benefit of their मजदूर.
निजी property can circumvent कया is अभी referred to as the “ tragedy of the कॉमन्स ” प्रॉब्लम, where people tend to degrade आम property more than they do निजी प्रॉपर्टी.
Given a short-sighted मालिक, however, a निजी प्रॉपर्टी system can मेक ये tragedies worse—for उदाहरण, a निजी मालिक of a टुकड़ा of oil-rich प्रॉपर्टी, depending on उसके worldview, might be more दिलचस्पी in short-term वित्तीय लाभ than वृद्धिशील use with an नजर toward अन्य 's चिंताएं ( e.g., those of भविष्य generations, the disenfranchised, इत्यादि. ).
While Aristotle जायज the अस्तित्व of private स्वामित्व, he बाएँ खोलें questions of ( 1 ) how to allocate property between what is private और common and ( 2 ) how to allocate the निजी property भीतर समाज.
Over the millennia, और आरपार संस्कृतियों what can be प्रॉपर्टी और कैसा it is regarded culturally have varied widely.
स्वामित्व is the basis लिये अनेक other अवधारणाओं that रूप the foundations of प्राचीन and आधुनिक societies ऐसे as धन, व्यापार, debt, दिवालियापन, the criminality of चोरी, और private vs. public property.
स्वामित्व is the key building ब्लाक in the विकास of the पूंजीवादी socio-economic प्रणाली.
Adam स्मिथ stated that one of the पवित्र कानून of इंसाफ थी to guard a person 's प्रॉपर्टी और possessions.
The प्रक्रम और यांत्रिकी of स्वामित्व are fairly जटिल : एक can gain, transfer and खोना स्वामित्व of property in a क्रमांक of ways.
To acquire property एक can खरीदें it with money, व्यापार it लिये other प्रॉपर्टी, receive it as a gift, चोरी it, find it, make, it or होमस्टीड it.
One can transfer or lose ownership of property by selling it लिये धन, exchanging it लिये अन्य प्रॉपर्टी, giving it as a तोहफा, होने robbed of it, it, or having it stripped इससे one 's स्वामित्व through विधिक means such as eviction, foreclosure, seizure, or लेने.
स्वामित्व is self-propagating in that the मालिक of कोई property होगा भी अपना the economic benefits of कि प्रॉपर्टी.
`` What 's my Name ? '' is a सोंग अंकित by barbadian recording कलाकार रिहाना, for उसके पांचवां स्टुडियो एल्बम Loud ( 2010 ).

a गणितीय constant is a खास number, usually a real number, that is `` significantly interesting in some way ''.
स्थिरांक arise in अनेक अलग क्षेत्रों of गणित, साथ स्थिरांक such as e ( गणितीय constant ) | and pi| occurring in ऐसे विविध contexts as भूगोल, क्रमांक theory और कलन.
What it means लिये a निरंतर to उठता `` naturally '', and कया makes a constant `` interesting '', is ultimately a पदार्थ of taste, और कुछ गणितीय constants are notable अधिक लिये historical कारण than लिये their मूलभूत गणितीय ब्याज.
the अधिक popular constants have been studied throughout the ages और computed to अनेक दशमलव places.
सब गणितीय constants हैं definable संख्याएँ और प्रायः हैं also computable numbers ( chaitin 's निरंतर होने a significant exception ).
चुनावों to the United राज्य सीनेट यहूद held on November 2, 2010, for 37 of the संयुक्त States सीनेट 's 100 सीटे.
( a special election on January 19, 2010 in मैसाचुसेट्स थी आयोजित पहले in the year. )
Thirty-four of the सीटे यहूद लिये six-year शर्तें to the सीनेट 's `` क्लास तीन '', और तीन यहूद खास चुनावों लिये shorter शर्तें.
of the 37 चुनावों, 19 featured लाज़िम Democrats ( 7 of whom रिटायर्ड or were पराजित in the प्राथमिक ) और 18 featured incumbent republicans ( आठ of जिसको retired or were पराजित in the प्राथमिक ).
After the previous चुनावों ( in 2008 ), the संयुक्त राज्य Senate थी composed of 58 डेमोक्रेट, 40 republicans, and 2 independents जो caucus साथ the डेमोक्रेट.
Republicans जीती four seats आयोजित by retiring डेमोक्रेट और Republicans पराजित two लाज़िम डेमोक्रेट.
इस थी the largest number of republicans gains चूंकि the 1994 चुनावों and also the पहला time चूंकि कि चुनाव that Republicans सफलतापूर्वक defended सब of their अपना seats.
इस थी the fourth लगातार election of `` क्लास 3 '' सीनेटरों जहाँ Democrats have failed to लाभ सीटे and the तीसरा consecutive mid-term चुनाव आयोजित in a अध्यक्ष 's first term जहाँ republicans have picked-up सीटे.
despite ये रिपब्लिकन विन्स, however, the डेमोक्रेट retained a majority of the सीनेट साथ 51 सीटे प्लस 2 independents who caucus साथ them, compared to the 47 Republicans.
a संक्रांति is an खगोलीय event कि occurs twice each साल as the सूर्य पहुँच its उच्चतम or न्यूनतम excursion relative to the celestial equator on the celestial sphere.
As a परिणाम, on the day of the संक्रांति, the सूर्य appears to have पहुँचे इसके उच्चतम or lowest सालाना ऊँचाई in the आसमान above the क्षितिज at लोकल सौर नून.
The word solstice is निकला इससे the लैटिन sol ( sun ) और sistere ( to stand स्टिल ), because at the solstices, the Sun stands स्टिल in declination ; कि is, the मौसमी गति of the Sun 's पाथ ( as seen इससे धरती ) comes to a रोकें पहले reversing direction.
The solstices, साथ साथ the equinoxes, are कनेक्ट with the सीज़न.
in अनेक cultures the solstices mark either the शुरूआत or the midpoint of शीत और summer.
the पद संक्रांति can भी be used in a broader sense, as the तिथि ( day ) when this occurs.
The day of the संक्रांति is either the longest दिन of the साल ( in summer ) or the shortest day of the साल ( in शीत ) लिये कोई प्लेस बाहर of the ऊष्णकटिबन्ध.
जेरी Lee लुईस ( born सितंबर 29, 1935 ) is an American rock and roll और देश म्यूज़िक singer-songwriter और pianist.
he is known by the nickname `` the कातिल '' और is प्रायः viewed as “rock & फेंकें 's पहला great जंगली man”.
An early pioneer of चट्टान and roll music, in 1956 Lewis made उसके पहला रिकार्डिंग at Sun Records.
`` Crazy बाहें `` sold 300,000 नक़ल in the दक्षिण, लकिन it थी उसके 1957 hit `` पूरे lotta Shakin ' Going On `` कि shot लुईस to fame विश्वव्यापी.
Lewis followed इस in कि वही साल जब he अंकित songs such as `` ग्रेट Balls of Fire ``, `` breathless `` और `` ऊँची School गोपनीय ``.
लुईस sold अधिक records than Elvis Presley at this समय.
However, Lewis ' rock 'n ' roll करियर faltered in the वेक of his marriage to his young cousin.
He had छोटी success in the charts following the कांड और उसके popularity जल्दी faded.
उसके सजीव प्रदर्शन शुल्क plummeted इससे $ 10,000 प्रति night to $ 250.
In the meantime he थी संकल्पित to gain back some of his popularity.
During the जल्दी 60’s he did n't have much चार्ट कामयाबी with few exceptions ऐसे as `` कया 'd i Say ``.

बाद रिकॉर्डिंग गीतों ऐसे as `` i 'm on आग '' लिये अनेक years साथ छोटी success, in 1968 Lewis made a परिवर्तन into country म्यूज़िक और had हिट्स साथ songs ऐसे as `` another प्लेस, another Time ''.
इस reignited his career और throughout the लेट '60s and '70s he regularly topped the country-western चार्ट.
उसके # 1 देश हिट्स शामिल `` To मेक Love मीठी लिये तुम ``, `` There Must Be More to प्रेम than This ``, `` Would You लो another मौका on me `` and `` Me और Bobby McGee ``.

In the 21st सदी Lewis continues to दौरे to ऑडियंस around the संसार and still रिलीज नई एल्बम.
एक ऐसे एल्बम, titled पिछला man खड़ा, is उसके बेहतरीन selling to तिथि at over a लाख नक़ल sold worldwide.
This थी followed by औसत Old man which रै प्राप्त कुछ of the best बिक्री of lewis’s करियर.
लुईस has had a दर्जन gold records in दोनो चट्टान और देश, won several ग्रैमी पुरस्कार, including a Lifetime Achievement पुरस्कार.
Lewis थी inducted into the चट्टान और फेंकें हॉल of Fame in 1986, and his pioneering contribution to the genre रै महरूम पहचाना by the rockabilly हॉल of Fame.
in 1989, उसके जीवन थी chronicled in the फिल्म ग्रेट Balls of आग, अभिनीत डेनिस Quaid.
In 2003, Rolling स्टोन पत्रिका सूचीबद्ध उसके बक्सा नियत सब Killer, No फिलर : The Anthology number 242 on उनके list of `` 500 महानतम albums of all time ``.
in 2004, वे ranked उसे number 24 on उनके list of the 100 महानतम Artists of सब समय.
