The Emancipation Proclamation was an order issued to all segments of the कार्यपालिका branch ( सहित the Army और Navy ) of the United States by अध्यक्ष अब्राहम lincoln on जनवरी 1, 1863, दौरान the अमरीकी Civil War.
it थी आधारित on the president 's संवैधानिक authority as कमांडर in chief of the armed शक्तियां ; it was not a law passed by Congress.
It proclaimed सब those enslaved in confederate territory to be forever free, और ordered the फौज ( और all segments of the कार्यपालिका शाखा ) to दावत as free all those enslaved in ten राज्य that were स्टिल in विद्रोह, यूँ applying to 3.1 लाख of the 4 million स्लेव in the U.S.
the उदघोषणा could not be enforced in areas स्टिल under rebellion, लकिन as the army took कंट्रोल of confederate regions, the स्लेव in those regions यहूद emancipated rather than लौटे to their मास्टर्स.
इससे 20,000 to 50,000 पूर्व स्लेव in regions where विद्रोह था already been subdued यहूद तत्काल emancipated, और over 3 लाख अधिक यहूद emancipated as the संघ army advanced.
The उदघोषणा did not लागू to the पाँच स्लेव states कि यहूद नहीं in विद्रोह, nor to most regions already controlled by the संघ फौज ; emancipation वहीँ would आइये बाद पृथक राज्य क्रियाएँ and/or the दिसम्बर 1865 ratification of the तेरहवीं amendment, जिससे made slavery illegal everywhere in the U.S.
the उदघोषणा did not compensate the owners, did not itself गैरकानूनी गुलामी, और did not मेक the ex-slaves ( called freedmen ) citizens.
It बना the eradication of गुलामी an सुस्पष्ट war लक्ष्य, in addition to the लक्ष्य of reuniting the संघ.
on सितंबर 22, 1862, lincoln had issued a preliminary उदघोषणा कि he would order the emancipation of सब slaves in कोई state of the Confederate States of अमेरिका कि किया नहीं return to Union control by जनवरी 1, 1863.
None लौटे, and the order, signed और जारी जनवरी 1, 1863, took effect except in locations जहाँ the संघ था already ज़्यादातर regained कंट्रोल.
The उदघोषणा outraged white southerners जो envisioned a रेस युद्ध, angered कुछ Northern डेमोक्रेट, सक्रिय anti-slavery शक्तियां, और weakened forces in यूरोपीय कि चाही to intervene to सहायता the confederacy.
It also lifted the spirits of अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी दोनो in the दक्षिणी और Northern राज्य, और led to many slaves escaping उनके मास्टर्स और कार्यशील पीछे संघ लाइनों in अनुक्रम to have उनके emancipation enforced.

a digital कैमरा ( or digicam ) is a कैमरा कि takes वीडियो or still छायाचित्र by रिकॉर्डिंग बिंब on an इलेक्ट्रॉनिक image सेंसर.
सबसे कैमरे sold आज हैं डिजिटल, और डिजिटल cameras हैं incorporated into many डिवाइस ranging इससे PDAs and मोबाईल phones ( पुकारा कैमरा phones ) to वाहनों.
डिजिटल और film कैमरे share an ऑप्टिकल system, typically using a lens साथ a परिवर्तनीय diaphragm to फ़ोकस लाइट onto an चित्र पिकअप device.
The diaphragm और शटर admit the सही राशि of लाइट to the imager, बस as साथ फिल्मी लकिन the चित्र pickup device is इलेक्ट्रॉनिक बल्कि than रासायनिक.
However, unlike film cameras, डिजिटल कैमरे can display images on a स्क्रीन immediately बाद being recorded, और store and हटाएँ बिंब इससे memory.
Many डिजिटल cameras can भी रिकार्ड moving वीडियो साथ ध्वनि.
कुछ डिजिटल cameras can crop and सिलाई तस्वीरें and perform अन्य elementary चित्र संपादन.

the American रेड क्रॉस ( ARC ), also known as the अमरीकी नेशनल Red Cross, is a humanitarian organization that provides emergency सहायता, disaster राहत और education अंदर the संयुक्त राज्य.
it is the designated U.S. affiliate of the International Federation of रेड Cross और रेड crescent Societies.
Today, in addition to घरेलू विपत्ति relief, the अमरीकी रेड Cross offers सेवाएं in पाँच other areas : community सेवाएं कि help the needy ; communications सेवाएं और सुकून लिये military सदस्यों and उनके परिवार सदस्यों ; the संग्रहण, प्रसंस्करण and वितरण of रक्त और रक्त products ; शैक्षणिक कार्यक्रम on preparedness, health, and safety ; and international राहत और development कार्यक्रम.
जारी a कॉरपोरेट चार्टर by the United राज्य Congress अंतर्गत शीर्षक 36 of the United राज्य कोड, Section 3001, the American नेशनल Red क्रॉस is governed by स्वयंसेवक और समर्थित by community donations, income इससे स्वास्थ्य and सुरक्षा training और products, और income from रक्त products.
the अमरीकी रेड क्रॉस is headquartered in Washington, d.c.

a rooster ( also पुकारा a cockerel or मुर्गा ) is a male gallinaceous bird.
it प्रायः refers to a male मुर्गा ( gallus gallus ).
नादान पुरूष chickens कम than एक साल बूढ़ा हैं पुकारा cockerels.
The term `` rooster '' originates in the संयुक्त States, और the पद is widely प्रयुक्त throughout उत्तर अमेरिका, as well as Australia और नई जीलैंड.
In the United किंगडम और आयरलैंड the older term `` cockerel '' is अधिक commonly प्रयुक्त.
`` Cock '' is in general use as the नाम लिये a male of अन्य प्रजाति of बर्ड, for example `` मुर्गा गौरैया ''.
`` roosting '' is the action of perching aloft to sleep at रात्रि, और is done by both लिंगों.
The rooster is polygamous, लकिन can not गार्ड several nests of eggs at एकबार.
He guards the general area where his मुर्गियां are nesting, और होगा attack other roosters कि डालें उसके territory.
During the दिन, he usually sits on a ऊँची पर्च, usually 3–5 feet बंद the ground to serve as a lookout लिये his झुण्ड.
he होगा sound a distinctive alarm कॉल if परभक्षी are nearby.
the Pokémon व्यापार Card खेल ( पोकीमॉन tcg ) is a collectible कार्ड game आधारित on the Pokémon वीडियो game series, first प्रकाशित in अक्तूबर 1996 by मीडिया Factory in जापानी.
In the US, it थी initially published by wizards of the coast, the कम्पनी that produces, in दिसम्बर 1998.
Nintendo took over publishing in जून 2003.
it is एक of Nintendo 's पिछला बाकी strong links to इसके विरासत as a playing card कम्पनी.
Land Rover is a अंग्रेजों car निर्माता with its headquarters in gaydon, Warwickshire, United किंगडम जिससे specialises in four-wheel-drive वाहनों.
it is भाग of the जैगुआर Land रोवर group, a subsidiary of tata Motors of इण्डिया.
it is the दूसरी oldest four-wheel-drive car brand in the world ( after जीपी ).
The Land Rover नाम थी originally प्रयुक्त by the रोवर कम्पनी for one विशिष्ट गाडी model, नामित बस the जमीन Rover, launched by रोवर in 1948.
over the following years it विकसित into a marque encompassing a दायरा of four-wheel-drive models, सहित the defender, Discovery, Freelander, दायरा रोवर, दायरा रोवर Sport and Range रोवर Evoque.
जमीन रोवर्स हैं currently समवेत in the कम्पनी 's Halewood और solihull पौधे, with research और development लेने प्लेस at jlr 's gaydon और whitley engineering centres.
Land रोवर sold 194,000 vehicles worldwide in 2009.
Although the ब्रांड originates इससे the असली 1948 मॉडल, जमीन Rover as a कम्पनी रै only existed चूंकि 1978.
Prior to this, it was a product लकीर of the रोवर कम्पनी जिससे was subsequently absorbed into the rover-triumph प्रभाग of the अंग्रेजों Leyland मोटर Corporation ( bl ) following Leyland मोटर निगम ’s कब्ज़ा of रोवर in 1967.
the ongoing वाणिज्यिक कामयाबी of the original Land रोवर श्रेणी मॉडल, and latterly the Range रोवर in the 1970s in the midst of bl’s well documented कारोबार troubles prompted the establishment of a पृथक जमीन रोवर company लकिन स्टिल अंतर्गत the bl छतरियाँ, remaining भाग of the subsequent रोवर समूह in 1988, under the स्वामित्व of अंग्रेजों Aerospace after the remains of अंग्रेजों leyland were टूटा up and privatised.
in 1994 रोवर समूह plc थी acquired by BMW.
in 2000, Rover समूह थी broken-up by BMW और Land Rover थी बेची to घाट Motor कम्पनी, बनने भाग of its Premier Automotive समूह.
In 2006 घाट खरीदा the रोवर ब्रांड इससे bmw for around £6 million.
इस reunited the रोवर and जमीन Rover ब्रांड्स for the पहला समय since 2000 when the रोवर समूह was broken up by BMW.
In जून 2008, Ford बेची दोनो जमीन रोवर और Jaguar Cars to tata Motors.

the कवर of the पहला dvd संकलन released by Aniplex of the नई कप्तान Shūsuke amagai चाप
the ninth season of the ब्लीच anime श्रेणी is नामित.

The विनियमन of prostitution in the United राज्य is नहीं among the enumerated शक्तियां of the संघीय सरकारी ; Under the दसवाँ Amendment to the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान, it is therefore exclusively the डोमेन of the states to परमिट, prohibit, or वरना regulate commercial sex, मगर insofar as कॉंग्रेस may विनियमित it as part of अंतरराज्यीय कॉमर्स साथ laws like the Mann अधिनियम.
In most राज्य, वेश्यावृति is माना a misdemeanor in the श्रेणी of public order अपराधों, a crime कि disrupts the अनुक्रम of a जातियाँ.
it थी at एक time माना to be a vagrancy अपराधों.
फिलहाल, Nevada is the तभी state to allow वेश्यालय prostitution, the शर्तें of जिससे हैं stipulated in the Nevada Revised statutes.
तभी 8 काउंटी फिलहाल contain active brothels.
All forms of prostitution हैं illegal in क्लार्क County ( which contains the Las vegas–paradise महानगर क्षेत्रफल ), washoe काउंटी ( which contains Reno ), कार्सन नगर, Douglas काउंटी, and Lincoln County.
The अन्य काउंटी theoretically allow वेश्यालय वेश्यावृति, लकिन some of ये काउंटी currently have no क्रियाशील brothels.
Street वेश्यावृति, `` pandering, '' और जीना बंद of the proceeds of a वेश्या remain illegal under नेवाडा विधि, as elsewhere in the country.
as साथ अन्य countries, वेश्यावृति in the United States can be विभाजित into three broad categories : street prostitution, brothel prostitution, और अनुरक्षण वेश्यावृति.
The ईस्ट coast of the संयुक्त राज्य, also ज्ञात as the Eastern Seaboard or the अटलांटिक seaboard and commonly shortened to East coast, refers to the easternmost coast of the संयुक्त States along the अटलांटिक समंदर.
the states जिससे have shoreline on the ईस्ट coast are, from उत्तर to south, the U.S. राज्य of Maine, नई हैम्पशायर, मैसाचुसेट्स, Rhode द्वीप, Connecticut, New यॉर्क, नई जर्सी, डेलावेयर, मेरीलैंड, वर्जिनिया, North कैरोलिना, South Carolina, Georgia, और फ्लोरिडा.
Richard milhous निक्सन ( जनवरी 9, 1913 – April 22, 1994 ) was the 37th President of the संयुक्त States, serving from 1969 to 1974, when he became the तभी president to इस्तीफा the दफ्तर.
Nixon had previously served as a रिपब्लिकन U.S. प्रतिनिधि और senator इससे कैलिफ़ोर्निया and as the 36th वाइस अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य from 1953 to 1961.
निक्सन थी born in yorba Linda, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
He graduated from Whittier College in 1934 और Duke University स्कूल of विधि in 1937, returning to California to अभ्यास law.
he और his बीवी, Pat निक्सन, स्थानांतरित to वॉशिंगटन to कार्य for the federal सरकारी in 1942.
He subsequently served in the United States Navy दौरान संसार War II.
Nixon was निर्वाचित in California to the हाउस of Representatives in 1946 और to the सीनेट in 1950.
उसके pursuit of the Alger hiss मामला स्थापित उसके प्रतिष्ठा as a अग्रणी anti-communist, and elevated him to नेशनल prominence.
He was the कार्यशील mate of Dwight D. आइज़नहावर, the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी अध्यक्षीय nominee in the 1952 election.
Nixon served लिये आठ years as वाइस president.
he waged an unsuccessful अध्यक्षीय campaign in 1960, narrowly खोने to John F. कैनेडी, and खोया a रेस लिये राज्यपाल of California in 1962.
In 1968, he ran again लिये the प्रेसिडेंसी and थी निर्वाचित.
Although निक्सन initially escalated अमेरिका 's involvement in the वियतनाम War, he subsequently ended u.S. भागीदारी in 1973.
Nixon 's विज़िट to the People 's गणतंत्र of China in 1972 खोली राजनयिक संबंध between the two nations, and he initiated détente और the Anti-Ballistic मिसाइल Treaty साथ the सोवियत संघ the same year.
domestically, उसके administration generally embraced नीतियों that transferred शक्ति इससे वॉशिंगटन to the राज्य.
Among other things, he launched पहलों to लड़ो कर्कट और illegal drugs, imposed wage और दाम नियंत्रण, enforced desegregation of कुछ Southern स्कूलों, और स्थापित the पर्यावरणीय Protection Agency.
Though he presided over the चंद्र अवतरण beginning with Apollo 11, he scaled वापस manned स्पेस खोजी.
He was re-elected by a भूस्खलन in 1972.
Nixon 's second पद देखी an Arab आयल embargo, the resignation of उसके vice अध्यक्ष, Spiro agnew, और a continuing श्रेणी of revelations परिचय the Watergate scandal और अन्य misconduct by members of the administration.
The scandal escalated, costing निक्सन much of उसके political support, and on अगस्त 9, 1974, he resigned in the face of लगभग निश्चित महाभियोग और हटाना इससे office.
After his resignation, he controversially प्राप्त a pardon जारी by उसके successor, जेराल्ड Ford.
in retirement, Nixon 's work as an elder statesman, authoring अनेक books और undertaking अनेक विदेशी trips, helped to rehabilitate his पब्लिक image.
he suffered a debilitating stroke on April 18, 1994, और died four days later at the आयु of 81.
Sertraline hydrochloride ( व्यापार names zoloft, Lustral ) is an antidepressant of the selective serotonin reuptake inhibitor ( SSRI ) class.
it was introduced to the मार्केट by फाइजर in 1991.
sertraline is primarily विहित for major depressive विकार in वयस्क outpatients as well as obsessive–compulsive, दहशत, और सोशल चिंता disorders in दोनो adults and children.
in 2011, it थी the second-most prescribed antidepressant on the U.S. retail मार्केट, with 37,208,000 prescriptions.
the efficacy of sertraline for depression is समान to that of older tricyclic antidepressants, लकिन इसके पक्ष प्रभाव हैं much less pronounced.
मतभेद साथ newer antidepressants are subtler और also ज़्यादातर confined to side प्रभाव.
Evidence suggests कि sertraline may कार्य बेहतर than fluoxetine ( Prozac ) लिये कुछ subtypes of depression.
Treatment of दहशत विकार साथ sertraline results in a significant decrease of the क्रमांक of panic हमले and in improved विशेषता of life.
For obsessive-compulsive विकार, sertraline is नहीं as effective as संज्ञानात्मक behavioral चिकित्सा ; the बेहतरीन results have been हासिल by combining ये दो treatments.
Although स्वीकृत for सोशल phobia और posttraumatic तनाव disorder, sertraline लीड to तभी modest improvement in ये conditions.
Sertraline also alleviates the symptoms of premenstrual dysphoric विकार और can be प्रयुक्त in sub-therapeutic doses or intermittently लिये इसके treatment.
Sertraline साझा the common पक्ष effects और contraindications of अन्य SSRIs, with ऊँची rates of nausea, अतिसार, अनिद्रा, और यौन side प्रभाव ; however, it does नहीं cause वज़न लाभ, and its effects on दोनो संज्ञान और vigilance are अपेक्षाकृत mild.
In गर्भवती महिलाओं taking sertraline, the ड्रग was उपस्थित in significant concentrations in fetal blood, और थी also associated with a उच्चतर rate of various जनम defects.
similarly to अन्य antidepressants, the उपयोग of sertraline लिये अवसाद may be associated साथ a उच्चतर रेट of suicidality.

सचिवालय ( कूच 30, 1970 – October 4, 1989 ) was an अमरीकी thoroughbred racehorse that in 1973 became the पहला U.S. Triple Crown चैंपियन in 25 सालो.
he set रेस रिकॉर्ड in सब तीन कार्यक्रम in the श्रेणी — the केंटकी डर्बी ( 1:59.4 ), the preakness stakes ( 1:53 ), और the belmont stakes ( 2:24 ) — रिकॉर्ड that स्टिल stand आज.
He is माना to be एक of the महानतम Thoroughbreds of सब time.
In 1999, ESPN क्रमित सचिवालय the 35th बेहतरीन खिलाड़ी of the 20th century, the highest रैंकिंग racehorse on the list url_http.
he ranked दूसरी पीछे man o ' War in the Blood-Horse 's सूची of the Top 100 u.S. Racehorses of the 20th Century.
सचिवालय थी sired by बिंदास Ruler out of somethingroyal, by princequillo.
he was foaled at The मर्ग in Caroline काउंटी, Virginia.
Like his प्रसिद्ध पूर्ववर्ती man o ' युद्ध, सचिवालय was a large शाहबलूत टट्टू and थी दिए the वही उपनाम, `` Big रेड. ''

a typical 12 V, 40 ah lead-acid car बैटरी
An ऑटोमोटिव बैटरी is a type of rechargeable बैटरी that आपूर्तियाँ electric उर्जा to an automobile.
Usually this refers to an sli battery ( starting, lighting, प्रज्वलन ) to शक्ति the starter मोटर, the lights, और the प्रज्वलन प्रणाली of a vehicle’s इंजन.
ऑटोमोटिव sli batteries are usually lead-acid प्रकार, और हैं बना of छह गैल्वानी कोशिकाएं in series to provide a 12 वोल्ट प्रणाली.
प्रत्येक cell provides 2.1 volts लिये a total of 12.6 वोल्ट at पूरा चार्ज.
Heavy vehicles such as राजमार्ग ट्रक or tractors, प्रायः equipped with डीज़ल इंजन, may have two batteries in श्रेणी लिये a 24 volt system, or may have समानांतर स्ट्रिंग्स of बैटरी.
lead-acid बैटरी are made up of प्लेटों of lead और पृथक plates of सीसे dioxide, जिससे हैं submerged into an electrolyte समाधान of परिचय 38 % sulfuric acid and 62 % जल.
This causes a chemical प्रतिक्रिया कि रिलीज electrons, allowing उन्हें to प्रवाह through conductors to उपज electricity.
As the battery discharges, the एसिड of the electrolyte reacts साथ the materials of the plates, बदलना उनके सतह to सीसे सल्फेट.
जब the बैटरी is recharged, the chemical प्रतिक्रिया is reversed : the सीसे सल्फेट reforms into lead dioxide और lead.
साथ the प्लेटों लौटी to उनके असली condition, the प्रक्रम may अभी be repeated.
Battery recycling of ऑटोमोटिव batteries reduces the need लिये संसाधन required for manufacture of नई batteries, diverts toxic सीसे from landfills, and रोकता risk of improper निपटान.
Full-time नियुक्ति is नियुक्ति in जिससे a व्यक्ति works a minimum number of घंटों पारिभाषित as such by his/her employer.
full-time नियुक्ति often आता साथ लाभ कि हैं नहीं typically offered to part-time, temporary, or flexible मजदूर, ऐसे as सालाना छोड़, sickleave, और स्वास्थ्य बीमे.
full-time कार्य are often considered करियर.
They generally pay more than part-time jobs, और प्रायः carry अधिक घंटों प्रति week.
The Fair मजदूर मानकों अधिनियम ( flsa ) does not define full-time नियुक्ति or part-time employment.
इस is a पदार्थ generally to be संकल्पित by the नियोक्ता ( US विभाग of मजदूर ).
The परिभाषा by नियोक्ता can vary and is generally प्रकाशित in a company 's कर्मचारी हैंडबुक.
कंपनियाँ commonly आवश्यकता इससे 30–35 or 40 घंटों प्रति सप्ताह to be defined as full-time और इसलिए eligible लिये लाभ.
full-time औकात varies between कम्पनी और is often based on the शिफ़्ट the कर्मचारी जरूर work दौरान each work सप्ताह.
the `` standard '' work week consists of five eight-hour दिनों, commonly served between 9:00am to 5:00PM totaling 40 घंटों.
जबकि a four-day सप्ताह generally consists of चार ten-hour days ; it may also consist of as छोटी as नौ hours for a total of a 36 hour कार्य week.
Twelve-hour शिफ्ट हैं प्रायः तीन दिनों प्रति week, जबतक the कम्पनी रै the इरादे of paying out the कर्मचारी ओवरटाइम.
ओवरटाइम is legally सशुल्क out anytime an कर्मचारी works more than 40 घंटों per सप्ताह.
the legal minimum लिये ओवरटाइम starts at Base Pay + one-half.
the increased payout is considered to compensate थोड़ा लिये the increased fatigue जिससे a person experiences on such long शिफ्ट.
शिफ्ट can भी be बहुत irregular, as in खुदरा, लकिन हैं स्टिल full-time if the जरूरी क्रमांक of घंटों is पहुँचे.
वहीँ हैं कुछ परिस्थितियों where a person जो needs full-time कार्य is dropped to part-time, which is sometimes a रूप of constructive dismissal to avoid paying बेरोजगारी benefits to a laid-off worker.

the नियंत्रित Substances अधिनियम ( सीएसए ) थी enacted into law by the Congress of the United राज्य as Title II of the व्यापक Drug गाली Prevention और कंट्रोल Act of 1970.
the सीएसए is the federal u.S. ड्रग policy अंतर्गत which the manufacture, importation, possession, use and वितरण of निश्चित substances is regulated.
The Act भी परोसा as the नेशनल implementing legislation for the सिंगल सम्मेलन on Narcotic Drugs.
the legislation निर्मित five Schedules ( classifications ), साथ varying योग्यता for a substance to be शामिल in each.
दो federal agencies, the ड्रग Enforcement प्रशासन and the खाना and ड्रग Administration, determine which substances हैं added to or removed इससे the various schedules, हालांकि the statute passed by कॉंग्रेस निर्मित the initial लिस्टिंग, और Congress रै sometimes अनुसूचित other substances through विधान such as the Hillory J. farias and Samantha Reid Date-Rape रोकथाम अधिनियम of 2000, which placed gamma hydroxybutyrate in अनुसूची I. वर्गीकरण decisions are required to be made on मापदण्ड सहित संभावित for गाली ( an अपरिभाषित पद ), फिलहाल स्वीकृत चिकित्सा उपयोग in उपचार in the United राज्य, और अंतरराष्ट्रीय treaties.
Maya numerals
Maya numerals हैं a vigesimal ( base - twenty ) numeral प्रणाली प्रयुक्त by the pre-columbian माया civilization.
the numerals हैं made up of तीन प्रतीकों ; शून्य ( shell आकार ), एक ( a बिन्दु ) and पाँच ( a बार ).
लिये उदाहरण, thirteen is written as तीन dots in a आड़ा row above दो horizontal लाइनों stacked ऊपर each other.
Lyndon baines जॉनसन ( अगस्त 27, 1908 – जनवरी 22, 1973 ), प्रायः referred to as lbj, was the 36th अध्यक्ष of the United States ( 1963–1969 ), a position he assumed बाद उसके सेवा as the 37th Vice अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य ( 1961–1963 ).
he is एक of only चार people जो served in सब four निर्वाचित federal कार्यालयों of the संयुक्त राज्य : Representative, सीनेटर, वाइस President, और President.
जॉनसन, a Democrat इससे Texas, परोसा as a संयुक्त राज्य प्रतिनिधि from 1937–1949 और as a सीनेटर from 1949–1961, सहित छह सालो as संयुक्त States Senate Majority नेता, दो as सीनेट Minority नेता और दो as Senate बहुमत Whip.
After campaigning unsuccessfully for the लोकतांत्रिक नामांकन in 1960, जॉनसन was asked by John F. Kennedy to be उसके running mate for the 1960 अध्यक्षीय चुनाव.
Johnson succeeded to the प्रेसिडेंसी following the assassination of जॉन F. कैनेडी on November 22, 1963, समाप्त Kennedy 's पद and was elected President in his अपना सही, जीतना by a विशाल हाशिया over Barry Goldwater in the 1964 चुनाव.
जॉनसन was greatly समर्थित by the Democratic पार्टी और as President, he was जिम्मेदार for designing the `` ग्रेट समाज `` legislation कि शामिल कानून कि upheld सिविल अधिकारों, पब्लिक प्रसारण, Medicare, medicaid, environmental protection, सहायता to education, और his `` War on गरीबी. ''
Johnson थी renowned लिये उसके domineering personality and the `` Johnson उपचार, '' उसके coercion of powerful राजनेता in अनुक्रम to अग्रिम विधान.
Meanwhile, जॉनसन escalated American involvement in the वियतनाम युद्ध, इससे 16,000 अमरीकी advisors/soldiers in 1963 to 550,000 कॉम्बैट सैनिकों in जल्दी 1968, as American casualties soared और the सलाम process bogged bas.
the भागीदारी stimulated a large एंग्री antiwar गति आधारित especially on university campuses in the u.S. और विदेश.
गर्मियाँ riots broke out in most प्रमुख शहरों after 1965, and crime दरों soared, as उसके प्रतिद्वंद्वियों raised demands लिये `` विधि और order '' नीतियों.
the लोकतांत्रिक Party split in multiple feuding गिरोहों, और बाद जॉनसन किया poorly in the 1968 नई Hampshire प्राथमिक, he ended उसके bid for reelection.
Republican रिचर्ड Nixon थी निर्वाचित to सफल उसे.
Historians argue कि जॉनसन 's प्रेसिडेंसी चिह्नित the peak of modern उदारतावाद in the United States बाद the नई Deal era.
जॉनसन is क्रमित favorably by some historians because of उसके domestic नीतियों.

the दूसरी crusade ( 1145–1149 ) थी the दूसरी major crusade शुभारम्भ इससे यूरोपीय.
the दूसरी Crusade थी started in response to the पतन of the County of edessa the पिछला year to the शक्तियां of zengi.
the काउंटी had महरूम founded दौरान the First crusade ( 1096–1099 ) by baldwin of boulogne in 1098.
While it थी the पहला Crusader राज्य to be संस्थापित, it थी भी the पहला to पतन.
The दूसरी crusade थी announced by Pope यूजीन iii, and थी the पहला of the crusades to be led by यूरोपीय किंग्स, namely लुई VII of France and Conrad III of जर्मनी, साथ सहायता इससे a number of other यूरोपीय nobles.
the armies of the दो किंग्स marched separately across Europe.
बाद crossing बीज़ान्टिन territory into आनातोलिया, दोनो सेना यहूद separately पराजित by the Seljuq turks.
the प्रमुख Western Christian source, odo of deuil, and syriac Christian स्त्रोत claim कि the Byzantine emperor Manuel i Comnenus secretly hindered the crusaders ' progress, विशेषकर in Anatolia जहाँ he is कथित to have deliberately ordered turks to attack them.
Louis और कोनराड और the remnants of their सेना पहुँचे जेरूसलम and, in 1148, participated in an ill-advised आक्रमण on दमिश्क.
the crusade in the east was a failure for the crusaders and a ग्रेट विजय लिये the Muslims.
it होता ultimately have a key influence on the fall of जेरूसलम और दे वृद्धि to the तीसरा Crusade at the end of the 12th सदी.
the तभी success of the Second Crusade आए to a संयुक्त फ़ोर्स of 13,000 फ्लेमिश, frisian, Norman, English, स्कॉटिश, and जर्मनी crusaders in 1147.
यात्राएं from इंग्लैण्ड, by ship, to the पावन Land, the फौज stopped और helped the छोटी ( 7,000 ) पुर्तगाली फौज in the capture of लिस्बन, expelling its मूरिश occupants.
wal-mart स्टोर्स, Inc. ( ), ब्रांडेड as walmart, is an American multinational retail निगम कि रनों chains of large छूट विभाग स्टोर्स and गोदाम stores.
The कम्पनी is the world 's तीसरा largest पब्लिक corporation, according to the Fortune Global 500 list in 2012, the biggest private नियोक्ता in the संसार with over दो लाख कर्मचारी, और is the largest retailer in the संसार.
walmart remains a family-owned business, as the कम्पनी is controlled by the Walton family, जो own a 48 प्रतिशत stake in walmart.
It is also एक of the संसार 's सबसे मूल्यवान कंपनियाँ.
the company थी founded by Sam वाल्टन in 1962, incorporated on October 31, 1969, and publicly traded on the नई York Stock एक्सचेंज in 1972.
It is headquartered in Bentonville, अरकंसास.
Walmart is भी the largest grocery रिटेलर in the संयुक्त States.
in 2009, it generated 51 प्रतिशत of इसके US $ 258 billion sales in the U.S. इससे किराना कारोबार.
it भी owns and operates the sam 's क्लबों खुदरा warehouses in North अमेरिका.
by 1988, wal-mart was the most लाभप्रद retailer in the US, और by November 1990, it outsold K-mart.
By 1991 it outsold Sears in खुदरा, बनाना it America 's largest retailer, a distinction it स्टिल holds.
Walmart has 8,500 stores in 15 देशों, अंतर्गत 55 अलग names.
The कम्पनी operates अंतर्गत the walmart name in the संयुक्त राज्य, सहित the 50 राज्य और प्यूर्टो रीको.
it operates in मैक्सिको as walmex, in the संयुक्त Kingdom as Asda, in Japan as seiyu, और in इण्डिया as Best दाम.
It has wholly owned operations in अर्जेंटीना, ब्राज़ील, और Canada.
Walmart 's investments outside उत्तर अमेरिका have था मिश्रित परिणाम : इसके परिचालन in the United Kingdom, South अमेरिका, और China हैं अत्यधिक कामयाब, whereas ventures in Germany and दक्षिण कोरियाई were unsuccessful.

an उदाहरण of रैक आरोहित servers
A वेब होस्टिंग सेवा is a प्रकार of Internet होस्टिंग सेवा कि allows individuals और संगठन to make उनके website accessible via the संसार चौड़ी वेब.
Web hosts हैं कंपनियाँ that provide स्पेस on a सर्वर owned or leased लिये उपयोग by क्लाइंट, as खूब as providing Internet कनेक्टिविटी, typically in a आंकड़ा center.
Web होस्ट can भी provide आंकड़ा center space और कनेक्टिविटी to the अंतरजाल लिये other सर्वर स्तिथ in उनके data बीच, पुकारा colocation, also known as आवास in Latin अमेरिका or फ़्रांस.
the पैमाना of web होस्टिंग सेवाएं varies greatly.
The सबसे मौलिक is वेब पेज और small-scale संचिका होस्टिंग, where फाइलें can be uploaded via File Transfer Protocol ( FTP ) or a वेब इंटरफ़ेस.
the फाइलें हैं प्रायः वितरित to the Web `` as is '' or साथ minimal processing.
Many अंतरजाल सेवा प्रदाताओं ( isps ) offer इस service free to सदस्य.
Individuals and संगठन may भी obtain वेब पेज होस्टिंग इससे alternative सेवा providers.
Personal वेब site होस्टिंग is typically फ़्री, advertisement-sponsored, or inexpensive.
Business web site होस्टिंग प्रायः रै a उच्चतर व्यय depending upon the आकार and type of the website.
सिंगल page hosting is generally sufficient लिये personal वेब पृष्ठों.
a complex site calls लिये a more comprehensive पैकेज that provides database support और अनुप्रयोग development platforms ( e.g. पीएचपी, जावा, माणिक्य on rails, coldfusion, or asp.net ).
ये facilities allow customers to लिखें or install scripts for applications जैसे forums and content प्रबन्धन.
भी, Secure sockets Layer ( एसएसएल ) is typically used for e-commerce.
The मेजबान may भी provide an इंटरफ़ेस or control फलक लिये मैनेजिंग the वेब सर्वर and installing स्क्रिप्ट, as खूब as other मौड्यूल और सेवा अनुप्रयोग जैसे e-mail.
कुछ hosts specialize in निश्चित software or services ( e.g. e-commerce ), which are commonly प्रयुक्त by larger कंपनियाँ कि outsource संजाल अवसंरचना.
obstetrics ( from the लैटिन obstare, `` to स्टैंड by '' ) is the चिकित्सा specialty dealing साथ the परवाह of all women 's reproductive tracts और their children दौरान pregnancy ( prenatal काल ), प्रसव और the postnatal period.

the राइट brothers, Orville ( अगस्त 19, 1871 – जनवरी 30, 1948 ) और wilbur ( April 16, 1867 – may 30, 1912 ), यहूद दो अमरीकी भाइयो, inventors, और विमानन pioneers who यहूद credited साथ inventing और building the world 's first कामयाब वायुयान and बनाना the पहला नियंत्रित, powered और sustained heavier-than-air इंसान उड़ान, on December 17, 1903.
इससे 1905 to 1907, the brothers developed their flying यंत्र into the first practical fixed-wing aircraft.
हालांकि नहीं the पहला to build और fly experimental वायुयान, the Wright भाइयो were the पहला to इफ़तेरा वायुयान नियंत्रण that made fixed-wing संचालित flight संभावित.
the brothers ' fundamental breakthrough was उनके आविष्कार of three-axis कंट्रोल, जिससे enabled the pilot to steer the aircraft effectively और to maintain its संतुलन.
This method became मानक और remains मानक on fixed-wing aircraft of सब kinds.
इससे the beginning of उनके aeronautical कार्य, the Wright brothers केन्द्रित on विकासशील a विश्वसनीय विधि of pilot control as the कुंजी to solving `` the flying प्रॉब्लम ''.
This दृष्टिकोण differed significantly इससे other experimenters of the time जो put अधिक जोर on विकासशील शक्तिशाली इंजन.
Using a छोटी homebuilt wind टनल, the wrights भी collected अधिक सटीक आंकड़ा than any पहले, enabling उन्हें to design and निर्माण विंग्स and propellers कि यहूद more कुशल than कोई पहले.
Their पहला u.S. पेटेंट, 821,393, किया नहीं claim आविष्कार of a उड़ती machine, लकिन rather, the आविष्कार of a प्रणाली of aerodynamic कंट्रोल कि manipulated a flying machine 's सतहों.
वे gained the mechanical कौशल अनिवार्य लिये their कामयाबी by working लिये सालो in उनके दूकान साथ मुद्रण दबाता, bicycles, मोटर्स, और other मशीनरी.
उनके कार्य with bicycles in particular बहकावे उनके belief कि an unstable गाडी like a उड़ती यंत्र could be नियंत्रित and संतुलित with अभ्यास.
इससे 1900 जबतक their पहला powered फ़्लाइट in लेट 1903, वे conducted extensive glider परीक्षण कि भी developed उनके skills as पायलटों.
Their bicycle shop कर्मचारी चार्ली टेलर became an महत्वपूर्ण part of the टोली, building their पहला aircraft इंजन in close collaboration with the brothers.
the Wright brothers ' औकात as आविष्कारक of the airplane has महरूम subject to counter-claims by विभिन्न पार्टियों.
Much controversy persists over the many स्पर्धा claims of जल्दी aviators.

Exxon mobil निगम, or exxonmobil, is an अमरीकी बहुराष्ट्रीय आयल and gas निगम headquartered in इरविंग, टेक्सास, United राज्य.
it is a direct descendant of जॉन D. Rockefeller 's मानक आयल company, और was formed on नवम्बर 30, 1999, by the विलय of exxon और Mobil.
it is संबद्ध with Imperial आयल which operates in Canada.
exxonmobil is the संसार 's largest कम्पनी by आय and in 2013, became the largest publicly traded company by मार्केट capitalization in the world.
The company is ranked # 5 globally in Forbes Global 2000 list in 2013.
exxon mobil 's reserves यहूद 72 अरब oil-equivalent barrels at the end of 2007 और, at then ( 2007 ) दरों of उत्पादन, हैं अपेक्षित to पिछला over 14 सालो.
साथ 37 आयल refineries in 21 countries constituting a संयुक्त रोज़ refining क्षमता of, exxon Mobil is the largest refiner in the संसार, a title कि थी भी associated साथ मानक आयल चूंकि its incorporation in 1870.
ExxonMobil is the largest of the world 's supermajors साथ रोज़ उत्पादन of 3.921 लाख boe ( barrels of आयल equivalent ).
In 2008, इस थी लगभग 3 % of world production, जिससे is less than अनेक of the largest state-owned petroleum companies.
जब ranked by आयल and गैस reserves it is 14th in the संसार with कम than 1 % of the total.
A 2012 article in the Daily टेलीग्राफ says that ExxonMobil has `` grown into one of the planet’s सबसे hated corporations, समर्थ to determine American विदेशी नीति and the भाग्य of संपूर्ण nations ''.
in शर्तें of इसके environmental record, exxonmobil increasingly drills in terrains leased to उन्हें by dictatorships, ऐसे as those in Chad और भूमध्यरेखीय गिनी.
Lee रेमंड, the corporation’s chief executive जबतक 2005, was `` notoriously sceptical परिचय जलवायु बदलें और disliked सरकारी हस्तक्षेप at कोई स्तर ''.
The company was widely criticized for its slow response to cleaning इसके 1989 valdez आयल spill in Alaska.

the ग्लोब थिएटर थी a theatre in लंदन associated with विलियम Shakespeare.
It थी built in 1599 by शेक्सपियर 's playing कम्पनी, the रब चेम्बरलेन 's Men, on जमीन स्वामित्व by थामस Brend and inherited by his बेटे, Nicholas brend और पोता Sir मैथ्यू Brend, and थी नष्ट by आग on 29 June 1613.
A दूसरी ग्लोब थिएटर थी निर्मित on the same साईट by जून 1614 and closed in 1642.
A modern पुनर्निर्माण of the ग्लोब, named `` Shakespeare 's ग्लोब ``, खोली in 1997 लगभग from the site of the original theatre.
it 's a अद्भुत जीवन is a 1946 अमरीकी क्रिसमस नाटक फिल्मी उत्पादित and directed by Frank Capra, based on the छोटी स्टोरी `` The महानतम तोहफा ``, which फिलिप वैन doren stern लिखा in 1939 और privately प्रकाशित in 1945.
The फिल्मी is considered एक of the सबसे loved films in American cinema और रै become परंपरागत viewing दौरान the Christmas season, alongside लोकप्रिय क्लासिक ऐसे as Charles डिकेंस ' a क्रिसमस कैरोल.
The film सितारों जेम्स Stewart as जार्ज बेली, a man जो has दिए up his dreams in अनुक्रम to सहायता अन्य और whose imminent आत्महत्या on क्रिसमस Eve brings परिचय the हस्तक्षेप of his guardian angel, Clarence odbody ( हेनरी ट्रेवर्स ).
Clarence shows जार्ज all the जीवनदान he रै छुआ और how अलग life in उसके community of Bedford जलप्रपात होता be था he never been born.
despite initially performing poorly at the बक्सा office due to ऊँची उत्पादन लागत and stiff competition at the time of its release, the film रै आइये to be regarded as a क्लासिक और is a स्टेपल of Christmas television around the संसार.
Theatrically, the फिल्मी 's break-even पाइंट थी actually $ 6.3 लाख, approximately twice the उत्पादन cost, a फिगर it never came बंद to achieving in इसके initial रिलीज.
an appraisal in 2006 reported : `` Although it थी not the complete box दफ्तर failure that आज everyone believes... it थी initially a प्रमुख disappointment and पुष्टि, at least to the studios, कि capra थी no longer capable of turning out the populist features कि बना his films the must-see, money-making events they once यहूद. ''
the फिल्मी was nominated for पाँच ऑस्कर और has महरूम पहचाना by the अमरीकी फिल्मी Institute as एक of the 100 बेहतरीन American films ever made, placing क्रमांक 11 on इसके आरंभिक 1998 महानतम फिल्म list, और होता भी प्लेस number one on its list of the सबसे inspirational अमरीकी films of all समय.
आंकड़ा गोदाम Overview
in computing, a data warehouse or एंटरप्राइज़ आंकड़ा गोदाम ( DW, dwh, or EDW ) is a डेटाबेस प्रयुक्त लिये रिपोर्टिंग और data analysis.
it is a central repository of data जिससे is निर्मित by integrating आंकड़ा इससे एक or अधिक disparate स्त्रोत.
आंकड़ा warehouses स्टोर current as खूब as historical data and हैं प्रयुक्त for बनाना चर्चित रिपोर्ट्स लिये वरिष्ठ प्रबन्धन रिपोर्टिंग ऐसे as सालाना and त्रैमासिक comparisons.
the आंकड़ा भंडारित in the गोदाम are uploaded from the operational प्रणालियों ( such as विपणन, sales etc., दिखाया in the figure to the सही ).
The आंकड़ा may pass through an operational data store for additional परिचालन before they हैं प्रयुक्त in the DW लिये रिपोर्टिंग.
the typical etl -based आंकड़ा warehouse uses स्टेजिंग, data संयोजन, और अभिगम परतों to house its key functions.
the स्टेजिंग परत or स्टेजिंग डेटाबेस स्टोर्स कच्चा आंकड़ा निकाली इससे प्रत्येक of the disparate सोर्स data प्रणालियों.
the संयोजन परत integrates the disparate data सेट by transforming the data इससे the staging परत often storing this रूपांतरित data in an operational आंकड़ा स्टोर ( ods ) database.
the एकीकृत आंकड़ा हैं then moved to yet another डेटाबेस, प्रायः पुकारा the आंकड़ा गोदाम database, जहाँ the data is arranged into hierarchical groups often पुकारा आयाम and into तथ्य और कुल facts.
the संयोजन of facts और आयाम is sometimes called a स्टार स्कीमा.
The access layer helps उपयोक्ता retrieve आंकड़ा.
a आंकड़ा warehouse constructed इससे an एकीकृत आंकड़ा source systems does नहीं आवश्यकता etl, स्टेजिंग databases, or operational data store databases.
The एकीकृत data सोर्स systems may be माना to be a part of a वितरित operational आंकड़ा स्टोर परत.
आंकड़ा संघ methods or आंकड़ा आभासीकरण विधि may be used to access the distributed integrated source data प्रणालियों to consolidate और कुल data directly into the आंकड़ा गोदाम डेटाबेस tables.
Unlike the ETL-based data गोदाम, the एकीकृत सोर्स आंकड़ा प्रणालियों और the आंकड़ा warehouse are all integrated चूंकि वहीँ is no transformation of dimensional or reference आंकड़ा.
इस एकीकृत data warehouse वास्तुकला supports the drill bas इससे the कुल आंकड़ा of the data warehouse to the transactional आंकड़ा of the एकीकृत source data systems.
आंकड़ा warehouses can be subdivided into आंकड़ा marts.
Data marts स्टोर subsets of आंकड़ा from a warehouse.
इस परिभाषा of the आंकड़ा गोदाम focuses on data storage.
the main सोर्स of the data is cleaned, transformed, cataloged और made उपलब्धियाँ लिये उपयोग by प्रबंधक और अन्य कारोबार पेशेवर लिये data खनन, ऑनलाइन analytical प्रसंस्करण, market शोध and decision support ( Marakas & O'Brien 2009 ).
however, the means to retrieve and analyze आंकड़ा, to निकालें, रूपांतरण और लोड data, और to मैनेज the आंकड़ा dictionary हैं भी considered essential components of a आंकड़ा warehousing system.
Many सन्दर्भ to आंकड़ा warehousing उपयोग this broader context.
यूँ, an विस्तारित definition लिये आंकड़ा warehousing शामिल business intelligence टूल्स, tools to extract, transform और load आंकड़ा into the repository, और tools to मैनेज और retrieve metadata.

an abandoned construction aggregate quarry निकट एडिलेड, South Australia
a quarry is a type of open-pit mine इससे which चट्टान or minerals हैं extracted.
Quarries हैं generally used लिये extracting building materials, such as आयाम स्टोन, निर्माण aggregate, riprap, बालू, और gravel.
They are often collocated with concrete और asphalt पौधे due to the आवश्यकता लिये विशाल amounts of कुल in those materials.
खोलें खानों कि उपज खनिज हैं typically referred to as खोलें गड्ढे खानों.
the शब्द पाषाण can शामिल भूमिगत quarrying लिये stone, such as Bath स्टोन.
mormons ( ) हैं a धार्मिक और सांस्कृतिक group related to mormonism, the प्रिंसिपल शाखा of the latter दिन संत movement of Restorationist Christianity, which began with the visions of Joseph Smith in upstate New York दौरान the 1820s.
बाद स्मिथ 's death in 1844 the Mormons followed ब्रिघम यंग to कया होता become the यूटा territory.
आज mormons हैं समझा to be members of The Church of यीशु Christ of Latter-day संतो ( LDS गिरिजाघर ).
Some mormons हैं also either स्वतंत्र or non-practicing.
The center of Mormon सांस्कृतिक influence is in यूटा, और North अमेरिका रै more mormons than any अन्य continent, हालांकि the बहुमत of Mormons सजीव outside the United राज्य.
mormons have विकसित a दमदार भाव of communality that तना from उनके doctrine और इतिहास.
दौरान the 19th century Mormon converts tended to gather to a सेंट्रल भौगोलिक स्थान, and between 1852 और 1890 a minority of Mormons खुलकर practiced plural विवाह, a form of धार्मिक polygamy.
Mormons dedicate विशाल amounts of समय and संसाधन to सेवारत in उनके गिरिजाघर, और many यंग Mormons चुनें to serve a full-time proselytizing mission.
mormons have a health कोड कि eschews alcoholic beverages, तम्बाकू, कॉफी, चाय, और अन्य addictive substances.
वे tend to be बहुत family-oriented, and have दमदार connections across पीढियां और साथ विस्तारित family, परावर्तक of उनके विश्वास कि families can be sealed साथ beyond मौत and throughout शाश्वत.
Mormons also have a सख्त law of शुद्धता, requiring abstention from यौन संबंध outside of विवाह and सख्त fidelity within marriage.
mormons self-identify as Christian, हालांकि some of their मान्यताओं differ इससे mainstream christianity.
Mormons मानना in the Bible, as well as अन्य किताबे of scripture, ऐसे as the Book of mormon.
वे have a अद्वितीय view of cosmology, and मानना कि सब लोगों are spirit-children of God.

In financial accounting, एसेट हैं economic संसाधन.
Anything ठोस or intangible कि is capable of होने owned or controlled to produce मान and that is आयोजित to have positive economic value is माना an एसेट.
बस stated, assets represent value of स्वामित्व कि can be परिवर्तित into cash ( हालांकि cash itself is भी माना an एसेट ).
The संतुलन चादर of a कड़ records the monetaryj.
G. siegel, N. Dauber & J. K. shim, `` the बनियान जेब CPA '', Wiley, 2005.There हैं अलग विधि of assessing the मौद्रिक value of the assets अंकित on the संतुलन चादर.
in some cases, the Historical Cost is used ; such कि the मान of the asset जब it was खरीदा in the पास्ट is प्रयुक्त as the monetary मान.
in अन्य instances, the उपस्थित मेला market value of the एसेट is प्रयुक्त to determine the मान दिखाया on the संतुलन चादर.
value of the assets स्वामित्व by the कड़.
It is धन and other valuables belonging to an individual or कारोबार.

intangible assets are nonphysical संसाधन and rights that have a मान to the कड़ because they दे the firm कुछ दयालु of लाभ in the मार्केट प्लेस.

a न्यूरॉन ( or ; also known as a neurone or तंत्रिका cell ) is an electrically excitable कोशिका कि प्रक्रियाओं और transmits सूचना through विद्युत और chemical signals.
a रासायनिक सिग्नल occurs via a अन्तर्ग्रथन, a specialized connection with अन्य cells.
Neurons कनेक्ट to प्रत्येक अन्य to रूप neural संजाल.
Neurons हैं the core components of the बेचैन प्रणाली, which शामिल the brain, स्पाइनल cord, और peripheral ganglia.
a number of specialized प्रकार of न्यूरॉन्स मौजूद : संवेदी न्यूरॉन्स respond to टच, ध्वनि, लाइट और numerous other stimuli affecting कोशिकाएं of the संवेदी organs that तब भेजें signals to the स्पाइनल cord and brain.
Motor न्यूरॉन्स receive signals इससे the दिमाग and spinal cord, cause muscle contractions, और affect ग्रंथियों.
interneurons कनेक्ट न्यूरॉन्स to अन्य neurons भीतर the same प्रदेश of the दिमाग or स्पाइनल cord.
a ठेठ न्यूरॉन possesses a cell body ( प्रायः पुकारा the सोम ), dendrites, and an axon.
dendrites हैं पतला structures कि उठता इससे the कोशिका देह, often extending लिये सैंकड़ों of micrometres और branching अनेक टाइम्स, giving वृद्धि to a जटिल `` dendritic tree ''.
an axon is a special cellular एक्सटेंशन that arises इससे the cell देह at a site पुकारा the axon hillock and travels for a अलहदा, as दूर as 1 मीटर in इंसानो or even more in other species.
the कोशिका देह of a neuron frequently देता वृद्धि to अनेक dendrites, लकिन never to अधिक than एक axon, हालांकि the axon may branch सैंकड़ों of times before it terminates.
at the majority of synapses, सिग्नल are भेजा इससे the axon of एक neuron to a dendrite of another.
There हैं, however, अनेक exceptions to ये rules : neurons कि lack dendrites, न्यूरॉन्स कि have no axon, synapses that connect an axon to another axon or a dendrite to another dendrite, etc.
All न्यूरॉन्स हैं electrically excitable, maintaining वोल्टेज gradients आरपार their झिल्लियों by means of metabolically चलित ion pumps, जिससे combine साथ आयन चैनल्स embedded in the झिल्ली to generate intracellular-versus-extracellular concentration मतभेद of ions such as सोडियम, पोटैशियम, chloride, और कैल्सियम.
परिवर्तन in the cross-membrane voltage can alter the फलन of voltage-dependent ion चैनल्स.
if the वोल्टेज changes by a large enough amount, an all-or-none electrochemical पल्स called an कार्रवाई संभावित is उत्पन्न, जिससे ट्रेवल्स rapidly along the कोशिका 's axon, और activates सिनेप्टिक connections with अन्य कोशिकाएं when it आगमन.
Neurons do नहीं undergo cell division.
In most cases, न्यूरॉन्स are generated by खास types of स्टेम कोशिकाएं.
astrocytes, a type of glial cell, have भी महरूम observed to फेरे into neurons by पुण्य of the stem कोशिका characteristic pluripotency.
In humans, neurogenesis largely ceases during adulthood—but in two दिमाग क्षेत्रों, the hippocampus और olfactory बल्ब, वहीँ is दमदार evidence for generation of substantial संख्याएँ of नई न्यूरॉन्स.
Super कटोरी XLIII was an अमरीकी फ़ुटबॉल खेल between the अमरीकी फ़ुटबॉल सम्मेलन ( afc ) चैंपियन पिट्सबर्ग स्टीलर्स and the नेशनल Football सम्मेलन ( NFC ) चैंपियन Arizona कार्डिनल्स to decide the नेशनल Football लीग ( एनएफएल ) champion for the 2008 season.
the स्टीलर्स defeated the कार्डिनल्स by the स्कोर of 27–23.
the खेल थी played on February 1, 2009, at Raymond James Stadium in tampa, Florida.
With this जीत, the स्टीलर्स became the first टोली to जीत छह सुपर प्याले.
पिट्सबर्ग, जो समाप्त the नियमित season साथ a 12–4 रिकार्ड, also जीती their दूसरी Super कटोरी in four सालो बाद जीतना Super कटोरी XL at the end of the 2005 ऋतु.
The कार्डिनल्स entered the खेल seeking their पहला NFL title चूंकि 1947, the longest चैंपियनशिप सूखा in the लीग.
The club became an अनपेक्षित winner दौरान the regular season, compiling a 9–7 record, और the playoffs with the सहायता of head coach केन Whisenhunt, जो थी the Steelers ' अप्रिय समन्वयक in सुपर कटोरी xl, और the re-emergence of क्वार्टरबैक Kurt Warner, जो was the Super कटोरी mvp in सुपर कटोरी XXXIV with his former टोली, St. लुई Rams.
पिट्सबर्ग कूद to a 17–7 मध्यांतर lead, aided by linebacker जेम्स हैरिसन 's Super Bowl record 100-yard interception return for a touchdown.
trailing 20–7 at the start of the चौथी quarter, एरिज़ोना scored 16 अनुत्तरित अंक, सहित wide receiver Larry Fitzgerald 's 64-yard touchdown रिसेप्शन, to लो the lead साथ 2:37 बाकी in the game.
But the स्टीलर्स marched 78 गज to स्कोर on चौड़ी receiver santonio holmes ' 6-yard game-winning touchdown catch with 35 seconds बाएँ.
holmes, जो caught नौ गुजरता लिये 131 yards और a touchdown, including four receptions लिये 73 गज on कि final game-winning drive, थी named Super Bowl MVP.
He became the छठे चौड़ी receiver to जीत the award, and also थी the तीसरा पिट्सबर्ग receiver to win the award, following Lynn swann and hines वार्ड.
Despite the वैश्विक वित्तीय crisis और सीमित amount of आनुषंगिक festivities कि हैं सामान्यतः आयोजित पहले the खेल, the एनबीसी टेलीविज़न संजाल ब्रॉडकास्ट आकर्षित an average u.S. audience of 98.7 million viewers, बनाना it the most देखी Super कटोरी in इतिहास to कि point.
a आरेख of the इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक spectrum, प्रर्दशित विभिन्न गुण across the दायरा of बारंबारता और wavelengths
The इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक वर्णक्रम is the दायरा of सब possible बारंबारता of electromagnetic विकिरण.
the `` electromagnetic वर्णक्रम '' of an object has a अलग meaning, and is बजाय the characteristic distribution of इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक radiation उत्सर्जित or अवशोषित by that particular ऑब्जेक्ट.
the electromagnetic वर्णक्रम extends इससे नीचे the कम बारंबारता used लिये modern रेडियो communication to gamma विकिरण at the short- wavelength ( high-frequency ) समाप्त, thereby covering wavelengths इससे thousands of kilometers bas to a भिन्न of the आकार of an अणु.
The सीमा लिये long wavelengths is the size of the ब्रह्मांड itself, while it is विचार that the छोटी wavelength limit is in the vicinity of the Planck लंबाई, हालांकि in principle the वर्णक्रम is अनन्त और निरन्तर.
सबसे भाग of the इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक spectrum are used in विज्ञान लिये spectroscopic and other probing interactions, as तरीके to study और characterize matter.
in addition, radiation इससे विभिन्न parts of the वर्णक्रम रै मिला many other उपयोग for संचार and निर्माण ( देखिए इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक radiation लिये more अनुप्रयोग ).

ब्रायोफाइटा is a परंपरागत नाम प्रयुक्त to refer to सब embryophytes ( जमीन पौधे ) कि do not have सच्चा vascular ऊतक और हैं इसलिए पुकारा ' non-vascular plants '.
कुछ bryophytes do have specialized ऊतकों लिये the हस्तांतरण of जल ; however चूंकि these do नहीं contain lignin, वे हैं नहीं considered to be true vascular tissue.
फिलहाल bryophytes हैं thought नहीं to be a प्राकृतिक or monophyletic group ; however the name is convenient और remains in उपयोग as a collective पद for mosses, hornworts, and liverworts.
Bryophytes उपज enclosed reproductive structures ( gametangia and sporangia ), but they produce neither पुष्प nor बीज, reproducing via बीजाणुओं.
the पद bryophyte आता इससे Greek βρύον, bryon, `` tree-moss, oyster-green '' + φυτόν - phyton `` संयंत्र ''.
a बैंको is a वित्तीय institution and a वित्तीय intermediary कि accepts जमा and चैनल्स those जमा into lending क्रियाएँ, either directly by loaning or indirectly through पूंजी बाज़ार.
a बैंको is the कनेक्शन between customers कि have पूंजी deficits and customers with capital surpluses.
Due to their influence भीतर a वित्तीय प्रणाली और an अर्थव्यवस्था, banks हैं generally अत्यधिक regulated in सबसे countries.
सबसे बैंको operate अंतर्गत a प्रणाली ज्ञात as fractional आरक्षित बैंकिंग जहाँ वे थाम only a छोटी आरक्षित of the निधि deposited और lend आउट the बाकी लिये profit.
They are generally विषय to न्यूनतम पूंजी आवश्यकताएँ which हैं based on an अंतरराष्ट्रीय set of पूंजी मानकों, known as the basel accords.
the oldest bank still in existence is मोंटे देई Paschi di Siena, headquartered in सियेना, इटली, which रै been operating continuously चूंकि 1472.
It is followed by berenberg Bank of Hamburg ( 1590 ) and sveriges riksbank of Sweden ( 1668 ).
Banking in its modern भाव evolved in समृद्ध शहरों of पुनर्जागरण Italy, such as फ्लोरेंस, Venice और जेनोआ.
in the history of बैंकिंग, a number of बैंकिंग dynasties —among them notably medici, fugger, welser, berenberg, baring and Rothschild —have निभाई a सेंट्रल role over अनेक centuries.
the Xbox is a video खेल console manufactured by microsoft.
it थी released on नवम्बर 15, 2001 in North अमेरिका, फ़रवरी 22, 2002 in जापानी, and कूच 14, 2002 in Australia and यूरोपीय.
it थी microsoft 's first foray into the गेमिंग कंसोल मार्केट.
as part of the sixth-generation of gaming, the एक्सबॉक्स competed साथ सोनी 's प्लेस्टेशन 2, Sega 's Dreamcast ( which stopped अमरीकी बिक्री पहले the एक्सबॉक्स गई on sale ), और निन्टेंडो 's gamecube.
The Xbox थी the first कंसोल offered by an American कम्पनी after the Atari जैगुआर stopped sales in 1996.
The एकीकृत Xbox सजीव सेवा launched in नवम्बर 2002 allowed players to खेल खेल online साथ a ब्रॉडबैंड connection.
it पहला competed साथ Dreamcast 's ऑनलाइन service लकिन बाद primarily competed with PlayStation 2 's online सेवा.
हालांकि these two हैं फ़्री जबकि Xbox सजीव जरूरी a सब्सक्रिप्शन, as खूब as broadband-only कनेक्शन जिससे was नहीं completely अपनाया yet, एक्सबॉक्स Live was a कामयाबी due to बेहतर सर्वर, सुविधाएँ such as a दोस्त सूची, and milestone titles जैसे हेलो 2 released in नवम्बर 2004, which is the best-selling Xbox वीडियो खेल और थी by दूर the सबसे लोकप्रिय ऑनलाइन खेल लिये सालो.
एक्सबॉक्स 's successor, the एक्सबॉक्स 360, थी शुभारम्भ in November 2005.
the Xbox थी discontinued in लेट 2005 in जापानी जहाँ बिक्री यहूद ग़रीब.
It was discontinued in late 2006 in Europe and early 2007 in North अमेरिका.
the पिछला Xbox game in यूरोपीय थी Tony हॉक 's प्रोजेक्ट 8 released in नवम्बर 2006, और the पिछला खेल in उत्तर अमेरिका थी मैडेन एनएफएल 09 released in August 2008.
support for out-of-warranty Xbox consoles थी discontinued on कूच 2, 2009, stating that कोई in-warranty repair now needed will not be undertaken.
एक्सबॉक्स अभिगम to Xbox सजीव थी stopped on अप्रैल 15, 2010.
the इन्जील According to जॉन ( Greek τὸ κατὰ ἰωάννην εὐαγγέλιον ), commonly referred to as the Gospel of John or simply John and प्रायः referred to in New Testament scholarship as the चौथी Gospel, is an account of the पब्लिक मंत्रालय of Jesus.
It begins with the witness and प्रतिज्ञान by जॉन the Baptist और concludes साथ the death, दफ़न, resurrection, और post-resurrection appearances of Jesus.
This account is चौथी of the canonical gospels, after the synoptics मैथ्यू, चिह्नित और ल्यूक.
राज्य कि the book derives from the गवाही of the ' शिष्य जिसको यीशु loved. '
Along साथ पीटर, the unnamed शिष्य is विशेषकर बंद to यीशु, और early-church tradition identified उसे as जॉन the apostle, एक of यीशु ' बारह रसूलों.
the gospel is closely सम्बन्धित in style और सामग्री to the three surviving epistles of जॉन such कि टीकाकारों दावत the four किताबे साथ, yet, according to सबसे आधुनिक scholars, जॉन थी नहीं the author of कोई of ये किताबे.
Recent Christian Scripture scholarship अधिक और अधिक has लगाई जॉन भीतर a first-century यहूदी context.
रेमंड E. Brown किया pioneering कार्य to trace the विकास of the परंपरा from जिससे the gospel arose.
The discourses seem to be concerned साथ the actual मुद्दे of the church-and-synagogue बहस at the time जब the इन्जील was लिखा.
it is notable that, in the gospel, the community स्टिल appears to define itself primarily against judaism, बल्कि than as भाग of a wider Christian गिरिजाघर.
हालांकि christianity started as a गति भीतर judaism, धीरे ईसाइयों and Jews became bitterly opposed.
John presents a `` higher '' christology than the synoptics, meaning कि it describes यीशु as the incarnation of the दैवी लोगो through जिसको all बाते यहूद बना, as the ऑब्जेक्ट of veneration, और अधिक explicitly as परमेश्वर incarnate.
तभी in जॉन करता यीशु talk at length about himself और his divine भूमिका, प्रायः shared with the disciples तभी.
विरूद्ध the synoptics, जॉन focuses largely on अलग चमत्कार ( सहित resurrecting lazarus ), given as लक्षण meant to engender आस्था.
synoptic elements ऐसे as parables and exorcisms are नहीं मिला in जॉन.
It presents a एहसास eschatology in which मोक्ष is already उपस्थित लिये the believer.
The plagues of Egypt ( ), also called the टेन plagues ( ) or the Biblical Plagues, यहूद ten calamities कि, according to the biblical Book of Exodus, इसराईल 's God, yahweh, inflicted upon Egypt to राजी Pharaoh to रिलीज the ill-treated israelites इससे गुलामी.
Pharaoh capitulated after the tenth प्लेग, triggering the exodus of the Jewish people.
the plagues यहूद designed to contrast the शक्ति of Yahweh साथ the impotence of मिश्र 's various gods.
Some टीकाकारों have संबद्ध several of the plagues with निर्णय on specific gods संबद्ध साथ the Nile, प्रजनन और प्राकृतिक phenomena.
the plagues of मिश्र हैं also mentioned in the कुरान ( 7,133–136 ).
According to the किताब of Exodus, परमेश्वर proclaims कि सब the देवताओं of Egypt will be judged through the दसवाँ and फाइनल plague:
John मार्टिन 's painting of the प्लेग of hail और आग ( 1823 ).
a role-playing खेल ( आरपीजी and sometimes roleplaying game ) is a game in which खिलाड़ी assume the भूमिकाएँ of वर्ण in a fictional setting.
खिलाड़ी take जिम्मेदारी लिये एक्टिंग आउट ये भूमिकाएँ भीतर a कथा, either through शाब्दिक एक्टिंग or through a प्रक्रम of structured decision-making or अक्षर development.
क्रियाएँ लिया भीतर many खेल succeed or fail according to a औपचारिक प्रणाली of नियम और guidelines.
वहीँ हैं several फ़ॉर्म of RPG.
The original form, sometimes पुकारा the tabletop RPG, is conducted through चर्चा, whereas in सजीव कार्रवाई role-playing खेल ( LARP ) players physically perform उनके characters ' actions.
In both of these फ़ॉर्म, an arranger पुकारा a खेल master ( GM ) प्रायः decides on the नियम and setting to be used and अधिनियमों as referee, जबकि प्रत्येक of the other players plays the भूमिका of a single अक्षर.
अनेक किस्में of RPG also मौजूद in इलेक्ट्रॉनिक मीडिया, ऐसे as multi-player text-based muds and उनके graphics-based successors, massively multiplayer ऑनलाइन role-playing games ( mmorpgs ).
role-playing games also include single-player ऑफ़लाइन role-playing वीडियो खेल in which खिलाड़ी control a अक्षर or team जो undertake quests, and may शामिल capabilities that अग्रिम using सांख्यिकीय यांत्रिकी.
ये खेल प्रायः share जमावट and नियम साथ tabletop rpgs, लकिन emphasize character उन्नति अधिक than collaborative storytelling.
despite इस variety of forms, some खेल फ़ॉर्म ऐसे as व्यापार कार्ड खेल and wargames कि are सम्बन्धित to role-playing games may नहीं be included.
role-playing कार्यकलाप may sometimes be उपस्थित in such games, लकिन it is नहीं the प्राथमिक फ़ोकस.
the term is also sometimes प्रयुक्त to describe लिए simulation खेल और exercises प्रयुक्त in शिक्षण, training, and अकादमिक शोध.
the American Civil War ( acw ), भी known as the War between the राज्य or simply the सिविल War ( देखिए नामकरण ), थी a सिविल war fought इससे 1861 to 1865 between the संयुक्त राज्य ( the `` Union '' or the `` North '' ) और अनेक Southern स्लेव राज्य कि घोषित their secession and formed the confederate राज्य of America ( the `` confederacy '' or the `` दक्षिण '' ).
The war had its उत्पत्ति in the समस्या of गुलामी, विशेषकर the एक्सटेंशन of गुलामी into the पश्चिमी territories.
Foreign powers did not intervene.
After four years of bloody कॉम्बैट that बाएँ over 600,000 सैनिको मुर्दे और नष्ट much of the दक्षिण 's अवसंरचना, the Confederacy collapsed, slavery थी abolished, और the मुश्किल पुनर्निर्माण process of restoring नेशनल एकता और guaranteeing rights to the freed slaves began.
In the 1860 presidential चुनाव, republicans, led by अब्राहम lincoln, opposed expanding slavery into United राज्य ' territories.
lincoln won, लकिन पहले उसके inauguration on कूच 4, 1861, सात cotton-based स्लेव states formed the confederacy.
outgoing Democratic अध्यक्ष James बुकानन और the आवक republicans rejected secession as illegal.
lincoln 's inaugural पता घोषित his प्रशासन होता नहीं initiate civil युद्ध.
आठ बाकी स्लेव राज्य जारी to reject काल्स for secession.
Confederate शक्तियां seized numerous federal forts within territory claimed by the Confederacy.
a Peace Conference failed to ढूँढें a compromise, और दोनो पहलू prepared लिये war.
the confederates assumed that European देशों यहूद so dependent on `` किंग कपास `` that they होता intervene ; none did और none पहचाना the नई confederate राज्य of अमेरिका.
hostilities began on अप्रैल 12, 1861, जब confederate forces fired upon फोर्ट Sumter, a key fort आयोजित by Union troops in South Carolina.
lincoln पुकारा for प्रत्येक राज्य to provide सैनिकों to retake the फोर्ट ; consequently, four more स्लेव states joined the confederacy, bringing their total to ग्यारह.
The Union जल्द controlled the border राज्य और established a naval blockade that अबोध the दक्षिणी economy.
the पूर्वी थिएटर थी inconclusive in 1861–62.
the पतझड़ 1862 Confederate अभियान into मेरीलैंड ( a Union राज्य ) ended with confederate रिट्रीट at the बैटल of antietam, dissuading British हस्तक्षेप.
Lincoln जारी the emancipation Proclamation, which made समाप्ति गुलामी a युद्ध लक्ष्य.
to the वेस्ट, by summer 1862 the संघ destroyed the Confederate river नेवी, तब much of उनके पश्चिमी सेना, और the संघ at vicksburg विभाजित the confederacy in two at the Mississippi River.
in 1863, रॉबर्ट E. ली 's confederate incursion उत्तर ended at the Battle of gettysburg.
Western successes led to Ulysses S. ग्रान्ट कमांड of सब संघ सेना in 1864.
In the पश्चिमी थिएटर, विलियम T. शरमन drove ईस्ट to capture अटलांटा और marched to the sea, destroying confederate infrastructure साथ the रास्ता.
The Union marshaled the संसाधन और जनशक्ति to आक्रमण the confederacy from सब दिशानिर्देश, और could afford to लड़ो battles of अपघर्षण through the Overland अभियान towards रिचमंड, the Confederate capital.
the defending confederate फौज विफल, अग्रणी to ली 's आत्मसमर्पण to Grant at appomattox अदालत हाउस on अप्रैल 9, 1865.
The American Civil War was one of the earliest सच्चा औद्योगिक युद्धों.
Railroads, the टेलीग्राफ, steamships, और mass-produced हथियार यहूद employed extensively.
The mobilization of civilian factories, खानों, shipyards, बैंको, परिवहन और खाना supplies सब foreshadowed संसार War I.
It remains the deadliest युद्ध in अमरीकी history, resulting in the मौतों of an अनुमानित 750,000 सैनिको और an undetermined number of civilian हताहत.
इतिहासकार जॉन huddleston estimates the मौत टोल at ten प्रतिशत of सब उत्तरी males 20–45 years old, and 30 प्रतिशत of सब Southern श्वेत males aged 18–40.
the definition of the संसार 's व्यस्ततम विमानक्षेत्र has been निर्दिष्ट by the एयरपोर्ट Council International in Geneva, स्विट्ज़रलैंड.
the ACI defines and उपायों the following three प्रकार of airport traffic:
यात्री traffic : कुल यात्री emplaned and deplaned, passengers in पारगमन गिने once
कार्गो ट्रैफ़िक : loaded और unloaded freight और मेल in metric tonnes
ट्रैफ़िक movements : अवतरण और take-offs of वायुयान
संसार War i ( wwi ) थी a वैश्विक युद्ध centred in Europe कि began on 28 जुलाई 1914 और lasted until 11 नवम्बर 1918.
it थी predominantly called the World युद्ध or the ग्रेट War from its occurrence जबतक the start of संसार War II in 1939, और the First संसार War or World युद्ध I thereafter.
it involved सब the world 's ग्रेट powers, जिससे were assembled in दो opposing alliances : the allies ( आधारित on the ट्रिपल entente of the संयुक्त Kingdom, France और Russia ) और the Central Powers ( originally the Triple गठबंधन of Germany, austria-hungary and इटली ; but, as Austria–Hungary था लिया the अप्रिय विरूद्ध the अनुबंध, Italy did नहीं डालें into the war ).
These alliances यहूद both reorganised and expanded as more राष्ट्र डाला the war : इटली, Japan और the United राज्य joined the Allies, और the उस्मानी साम्राज्य और बुल्गारिया the सेंट्रल शक्तियां.
ultimately, more than 70 लाख military कर्मियों, including 60 million Europeans, were mobilised in एक of the largest wars in इतिहास.
अधिक than 9 लाख combatants यहूद मारे, largely क्युकी of technological advancements कि led to विशाल increases in the lethality of हथियार बगैर corresponding सुधार in सुरक्षा or गतिशीलता.
It was the fifth- deadliest विरोध in संसार इतिहास, subsequently paving the रास्ता लिये various political changes, such as revolutions in many of the nations शामिल.
One of the long-term कल्याणकारी of the war was the पुनरुत्थान of साम्राज्यवाद in the विदेशी policies of the ग्रेट powers of यूरोपीय.
अधिक immediately, the assassination of archduke फ्रांज Ferdinand of ऑस्ट्रिया, the वारिस to the सिंहासन of austria-hungary, on 28 जून 1914 by यूगोस्लाव nationalist gavrilo Princip in Sarajevo triggered a diplomatic संकट जब austria-hungary subsequently वितरित an ultimatum to the किंगडम of सर्बिया.
Several alliances formed over the previous decades were invoked.
भीतर सप्ताह, the major शक्तियां यहूद at युद्ध और, via their colonies, the conflict जल्द स्प्रेड around the world.
On 28 जुलाई, the austro-hungarians fired the पहला shots of the war as तैयारी लिये the आक्रमण of Serbia.
जबकि the Russians mobilised, the Germans invaded न्यूट्रल बेल्जियम और ध्वज on the रास्ता to France, providing a casus belli for Britain 's घोषणा of युद्ध विरूद्ध Germany.
After the जर्मनी कूच on Paris was brought to a halt—the so-called Miracle of the marne —the Western सामने settled into a स्थिर बैटल of अपघर्षण साथ a trench लकीर that changed little जबतक 1917.
on the Eastern Front, the रूसी army थी कामयाब विरूद्ध the austro-hungarians, लकिन was रोका in its आक्रमण of ईस्ट prussia by the germans.
in नवम्बर the उस्मानी Empire joined the war, खोलने up fronts in the काकेशस, मेसोपोटामिया and the Sinai.
इटली और बुल्गारिया गई to युद्ध in 1915 और Romania in 1916.
in Russia, the tsar 's government collapsed in कूच 1917 और a subsequent revolution in नवम्बर brought the russians to शर्तें साथ the Central शक्तियां.
बाद a 1918 German अप्रिय along the पश्चिमी front, the allies drove back the germans in a श्रेणी of successful offensives and American शक्तियां began प्रवेश the trenches.
Germany, which था इसके own trouble साथ revolutionaries, सहमत to an armistice on 11 November 1918.
the युद्ध ended in विजय लिये the allies.
Events on the घर fronts were as उग्र as on the battle fronts, as the participants आजमाया to mobilize their जनशक्ति और आर्थिक resources to लड़ो a कुल युद्ध.
by the समाप्त of the युद्ध, four major imperial powers—the जर्मनी, रूसी, austro-hungarian और Ottoman empires—ceased to exist.
the successor states of the former दो खोया a ग्रेट राशि of territory, while the latter दो यहूद dismantled entirely.
the map of सेंट्रल यूरोपीय was redrawn into अनेक छोटी states.
the लीग of Nations थी formed in the hope of preventing another ऐसे विरोध.
the European राष्ट्रवाद शाखित by the war और the ब्रेकअप of empires, the परखना of जर्मनी 's defeat और problems साथ the Treaty of versailles are सहमत to be factors contributing to World War ii.
The Deepwater Horizon oil spill ( भी referred to as the BP आयल spill, the BP oil विपत्ति, the Gulf of मैक्सिको आयल spill, and the macondo blowout ) थी an oil spill in the Gulf of Mexico on the BP -operated macondo Prospect, माना the largest accidental marine oil spill in the इतिहास of the पेट्रोलियम industry, estimated to be between 8 % and 31 % larger in volume than the पहले Ixtoc i आयल spill.
following the विस्फोट और डूब of the deepwater क्षितिज oil रिग, जिससे claimed 11 जीवनदान, a sea-floor आयल gusher flowed unabated for 87 दिनों, जबतक it was capped on 15 July 2010.
the कुल निर्वहन is estimated at.
a massive response ensued to protect beaches, वेटलैंड्स and मुहानों इससे the spreading आयल utilizing skimmer जहाजों, floating booms, controlled burns and of Corexit आयल dispersant.
बाद अनेक विफल efforts to contain the प्रवाह, the खूब थी घोषित sealed on 19 सितंबर 2010.
कुछ reports indicate the खूब site continues to लीक.
due to the months-long spill, साथ साथ adverse प्रभाव इससे the जवाब and क्लीनअप क्रियाएँ, extensive damage to समुद्री and wildlife habitats, फ़िशिंग और tourism उद्योग, और इंसान health problems have जारी through 2013.Three सालो बाद the spill, तारकोल balls could स्टिल be मिला on the मिसिसिपी coast.
numerous investigations छान the कल्याणकारी of the विस्फोट और record-setting spill.
notably, the u.S. सरकारी 's सितंबर 2011 report pointed to defective सीमेंट on the खूब, faulting mostly bp, but भी खूब ऑपरेटर Transocean और ठेकेदार halliburton.
पहले in 2011, a White हाउस आयोग likewise blamed bp और its partners लिये a series of cost-cutting निर्णय और an insufficient सुरक्षा system, लकिन also concluded that the spill resulted इससे `` systemic '' रूट causes and `` अनुपस्थित significant reform in दोनो industry practices और सरकारी policies, might well recur ''.
in November 2012, BP and the संयुक्त राज्य Department of इंसाफ settled संघीय दण्ड आरोप with bp pleading अपराधी to 11 counts of manslaughter, two misdemeanors, and a felony count of lying to Congress.
bp भी agreed to चार सालो of government निगरानी of its सुरक्षा practices और आचार, and the पर्यावरणीय Protection Agency announced कि BP would be temporarily बैन from new अनुबंध साथ the us सरकारी.
bp और the विभाग of इंसाफ सहमत to a record-setting $ 4.525 billion in जुर्माना and अन्य payments but further legal proceedings not expected to conclude जबतक 2014 are ongoing to determine payouts and fines अंतर्गत the Clean जल अधिनियम and the प्राकृतिक संसाधन क्षति मूल्यांकन.
as of फ़रवरी 2013, दण्ड and civil settlements और payments to a trust fund था लागत the कम्पनी $ 42.2 billion.
`` जहाँ the गलियों have No Name '' is a song by rock बैंड U2.
it is the opening track इससे their 1987 album the जोशुआ पेड़ and थी released as the album 's third सिंगल in August 1987.
the song 's आँकड़ा is a repeating गिटार arpeggio using a delay प्रभाव, निभाई दौरान the सोंग 's introduction and again at the समाप्त.
सीसे vocalist बोनो लिखा the गीत in जवाब to the notion कि it is संभावित to पहचानो a person 's religion और income based on the गली on which they जिया, particularly in belfast.
During the band 's कठिनाइयों recording the सोंग, निर्माता ब्रायन Eno considered erasing the सोंग 's टेपों to have them start from खरोंच.

The सोंग रै become एक of the band 's most लोकप्रिय गीतों and रै remained a स्टेपल of उनके live act since the सोंग debuted in 1987 on the जोशुआ Tree दौरे.

Thomas जेफरी `` tom '' Hanks ( born जुलाई 9, 1956 ) is an अमरीकी कर्ता, producer, लेखक, और निदेशक.

he has earned और महरूम nominated for numerous पुरस्कार during his career, सहित जीतना a सुनहरी Globe for Best कर्ता और an अकादमी पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन Actor लिये his role in Philadelphia और a Golden Globe, an अकादमी पुरस्कार, a Screen Actors Guild पुरस्कार, और a People 's चुनाव पुरस्कार for बेहतरीन Actor लिये उसके भूमिका in फॉरेस्ट गंप, और कमाई the स्टेनली Kubrick britannia पुरस्कार for Excellence in फिल्मी इससे the BAFTAs in 2004.

The केप is an American सुपरहीरो नाटक श्रेणी.
It premiered on एनबीसी दौरान the 2010–2011 television season as a mid-season बदलना शुरूआत साथ a two-hour पायलट एपीसोड on संडे, January 9, 2011 at 9 pm Eastern और प्रशांत समय.

Halley 's धूमकेतु or Comet हैली ( or ), officially designated 1P/Halley, is the best-known of the short-period धूमकेतुओं और is दृश्य इससे धरती every 75–76 सालो.
हैली is the only short-period धूमकेतु कि is clearly दृश्य to the नग्न eye इससे धरती, and यूँ the तभी naked-eye comet कि might appear twice in a human आजीवन.
अन्य naked-eye धूमकेतुओं may be उज्जवल and अधिक spectacular, but होगा appear तभी once in हज़ारों of years.
हैली 's रिटर्न to the भीतरी Solar System have been observed and अंकित by खगोलशास्त्रियों चूंकि at least 240 BCE.
साफ रिकॉर्ड of the comet 's दिखावे यहूद made by Chinese, babylonian, और medieval यूरोपीय chroniclers, but were नहीं पहचाना as reappearances of the वही object at the समय.
the धूमकेतु 's periodicity थी पहला संकल्पित in 1705 by अंग्रेज़ी astronomer edmond हैली, बाद जिसको it is अभी नामित.
Halley 's Comet last appeared in the भीतरी सौर प्रणाली in 1986 and होगा next appear in mid-2061.
दौरान इसके 1986 apparition, Halley became the first धूमकेतु to be observed in detail by spacecraft, providing the पहला observational data on the ढांचा of a comet केंद्रक and the यांत्रिकी of coma and tail formation.
ये observations supported a क्रमांक of longstanding hypotheses परिचय धूमकेतु निर्माण, particularly फ्रेड whipple 's `` dirty snowball '' मॉडल, which correctly predicted कि Halley would be रचित of a mixture of volatile ices – such as जल, कार्बन डाइऑक्साइड and अमोनिया – और धूल.

A California घरेलू साझेदारी is a legal relationship available to same-sex couples, and to certain opposite-sex युगल in which at तनिक one party is at तनिक 18 years of आयु.

Enacted in 1999, the घरेलू partnership रजिस्ट्री थी the first of इसके दयालु in the United राज्य created by a legislature बगैर अदालत हस्तक्षेप.

As ऐसे, कैलिफ़ोर्निया घरेलू partnerships are functionally equivalent to civil unions offered in several अन्य राज्य.
Although the program enjoys व्यापक support in कैलिफ़ोर्निया, it रै महरूम the सोर्स of कुछ controversy.
समूह opposed to the recognition of same-sex families have challenged the विस्तार of घरेलू partnerships in court.
conversely, advocates of same-sex marriage contend कि anything less than full विवाह अधिकारों विस्तारित to same-sex partners is analogous to the `` पृथक लकिन बराबर '' racial laws of the Jim Crow era.

दक्षिण Africa रै ग्यारह official languages : अफ्रीकी, अंग्रेज़ी, ndebele, Northern sotho, Sotho, Swazi, Tswana, Tsonga, Venda, ख़ोसा और Zulu.
Fewer than दो percent of दक्षिण africans speak a first भाषा अन्य than an आधिकारिक एक.
Most दक्षिण africans can बोलो अधिक than one भाषा.
Dutch and English यहूद the पहला आधिकारिक भाषाएं of दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी इससे 1910 to 1925.
Afrikaans was added as a भाग of डच in 1925.
डच was replaced by अफ्रीकी when South अफ़्रीकी became a republic in 1961, और Dutch was dropped in 1983, so between 1983 and 1994, दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी था दो official languages : English and अफ्रीकी.
the अंग्रेज़ी version of the South अफ़्रीकी संविधान refers to the भाषाएं by the names in those भाषाएं : isiZulu, isixhosa, Afrikaans, Sepedi ( referring to उत्तरी sotho ), setswana, English, sesotho ( referring to दक्षिणी sotho ), xitsonga, Siswati, tshivenda and isindebele ( referring to Southern ndebele ).
In South अफ़्रीकी, दक्षिणी Ndebele is known बस as ndebele, as सबसे अध्यक्षों of उत्तरी ndebele सजीव in ज़िम्बाब्वे.
the 1993 संस्करण of the संविधान referred to उत्तरी sotho as Sesotho sa leboa, लकिन the 1996 संस्करण referred to the भाषा as sepedi.
Different सरकारी departments और आधिकारिक लाशें use अलग terms to denote Northern sotho.
The प्रमुख भाषा of सरकारी is English भी if दक्षिण africans प्रायः take pride in using स्वदेशी भाषाएं for कोई purpose.
अफ्रीकी भी features prominently in commerce साथ with English as the भाषाएं with the उच्चतम number of धाराप्रवाह अध्यक्षों हैं अफ्रीकी और अंग्रेज़ी.
in शर्तें of भाषाई वर्गीकरण, the आधिकारिक भाषाएं include दो West-Germanic भाषाएं ( अंग्रेज़ी और अफ्रीकी ) और nine bantu भाषाएं.
चार of ये हैं nguni languages ( Zulu, Xhosa, स्वाति और ndebele ) और three are sotho–tswana languages ( उत्तरी sotho, दक्षिणी Sotho and tswana ).
Tsonga is a tswa–ronga भाषा.
दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी Sign भाषा is a distinct though incompletely उभरा नेशनल मानक भाषा जिससे also subsumes a cluster of semi-standardised dialects.

psilocybe semilanceata
psilocybin मशरूम, भी ज्ञात as साइकेडेलिक मशरूम, हैं fungi that contain psychoactive indole alkaloids.
वहीँ are multiple colloquial शर्तें लिये psilocybin मशरूम, the सबसे common होने shrooms और जादू मशरूम.

वहीँ हैं लगभग 190 प्रजाति of psilocybin mushrooms और सबसे of उन्हें पतन in the genus psilocybe.
Psilocybin मशरूम have likely महरूम प्रयुक्त चूंकि prehistoric टाइम्स और may have been चित्रित in rock art.
Many संस्कृतियों have प्रयुक्त these मशरूम in religious संस्कार.
in आधुनिक पश्चिमी society they हैं used recreationally लिये उनके साइकेडेलिक effects.
हाल अध्ययन किया at Imperial कॉलेज London और जॉन्स हॉपकिंस स्कूल of आयुर्विज्ञान conclude कि when used properly, psilocybin अधिनियमों as an anti-depressant as सुझाया by fmri दिमाग scans.
Alaska ( ) is a राज्य in the संयुक्त राज्य, situated in the उत्तरपश्चिम extremity of the North अमरीकी महाद्वीप, with the अंतरराष्ट्रीय boundary साथ Canada to the ईस्ट, the आर्कटिक Ocean to the उत्तर, और the प्रशांत समंदर to the वेस्ट and south, साथ Russia further west आरपार the Bering Strait.
अलास्का is the largest state in the संयुक्त States by क्षेत्रफल, the 4th least populous and the तनिक densely populated of the 50 संयुक्त राज्य.
Approximately हाफ of Alaska 's 731,449 residents सजीव भीतर the anchorage महानगर क्षेत्रफल.
Alaska 's अर्थव्यवस्था is dominated by the oil, प्राकृतिक गैस, और फ़िशिंग industries ; it रै these संसाधन in प्रचुरता.
Alaska was खरीदा from रूस on March 30, 1867, लिये $ 7.2 लाख ( $ समायोजित लिये inflation ) at approximately दो cents per एकड़ ( $ 4.74/km2 ).
the जमीन went through several administrative changes before बनने an organized ( or incorporated ) territory on may 11, 1912, and the 49th राज्य of the U.S. on जनवरी 3, 1959.
the नाम `` Alaska '' ( аляска ) was already introduced in the Russian colonial period, when it was प्रयुक्त तभी for the peninsula और is derived from the aleut alaxsxaq, अर्थ `` the mainland '' or, अधिक literally, `` the ऑब्जेक्ट towards which the कार्रवाई of the समुद्र is directed ''.
it is also ज्ञात as Alyeska, the `` great जमीन '', an aleut शब्द derived from the same root.
The 101 फ्रेंच विभाग हैं विभाजित into 342 arrondissements, which may be translated into English as जिले.
The पूंजी of an arrondissement/district is called a subprefecture.
When an arrondissement contains the prefecture ( पूंजी ) of the department, कि प्रीफ़ेक्चर is the पूंजी of the arrondissement, एक्टिंग दोनो as a prefecture and as a subprefecture.
arrondissements हैं further divided into cantons और communes.

in इंसानो, this ड्योढ़ी लीड from the opening of the भग to the uterus ( गर्भ ), लकिन the vaginal ट्रैक्ट ends at the ग्रीवा.
Unlike मेन, जो have तभी एक genital orifice, महिलाओं have two, the urethra और the योनि.
The vaginal खोलने is much larger than the urethral opening, और दोनो openings हैं सुरक्षित by the labia.

During arousal, the vagina gets नम to सुकर the प्रवेश of the penis.
The Latinate बहुवचन `` vaginae '' is rarely used in English.
colloquially, the word vagina is often प्रयुक्त to refer to the भग or to the मादा गुप्तांग in सामान्य.
However, by इसके dictionary and anatomical परिभाषाएं, vagina refers exclusively to the विशिष्ट आतंरिक ढांचा.

A prank stink bomb.
a stink bomb is a यंत्र designed to create an अप्रिय smell.
They दायरा in effectiveness इससे सरल pranks to सैन्य ग्रेड malodorants or riot कंट्रोल chemical एजेंटों.
the Guinness Book of Records सूचियाँ दो smelliest substances.
एक is `` US Government Standard बाथरूम Malodor '' ; a mixture of आठ chemicals साथ a stench resembling इंसान मल, only much stronger, designed to test the efficacy of deodorizers and एयर fresheners.
another एक, `` Who me ? ``, is a mixture of पाँच sulfur-containing रसायन और smells like rotting खाना and carcasses.
the adage `` a picture is लायक a हजार शब्द '' refers to the notion कि a complex विचार can be conveyed साथ बस a सिंगल स्टिल चित्र.
It भी aptly characterizes एक of the प्रमुख लक्ष्य of visualization, namely making it possible to absorb विशाल amounts of आंकड़ा quickly.
the expression `` उपयोग a चित्र.
it 's लायक a हजार words. '' appears in a 1911 newspaper आलेख quoting newspaper एडिटर आर्थर ब्रिसबेन discussing journalism and publicity.
1913 newspaper advertisement
A similar phrase, `` एक dekh Is लायक A Thousand Words '', appears in a 1913 newspaper विज्ञापन लिये the Piqua Auto Supply हाउस of piqua, Ohio.
an जल्दी उपयोग of the सटीक phrase appears in an 1918 समाचारपत्र विज्ञापन लिये the San अंतोनियो लाइट which says : एक of the Nation 's महानतम Editors says : एक चित्र is Worth a हजार शब्द the सैन अंतोनियो Light 's Pictorial Magazine of the युद्ध Exemplifies the सच्चाई of the above बयान -- judging इससे the warm reception it रै प्राप्त at the हैंड्स of the Sunday लाइट पाठक.
it is believed by some कि the आधुनिक उपयोग of the phrase तना from an article by फ्रेड R. Barnard in the विज्ञापन व्यापार जर्नल मुद्रक ' Ink, promoting the use of images in विज्ञापन कि appeared on the पहलू of streetcars.
The दिसम्बर 8, 1921 issue carries an ad हकदार, `` एक Look is लायक a Thousand शब्द. ''
another ad by बर्नार्ड appears in the March 10, 1927 issue साथ the phrase `` एक Picture Worth टेन हजार शब्द, '' where it is labeled a चाइनीज कहावत ( 一圖勝萬言 ).
The Home Book of proverbs, maxims, and Familiar Phrases quotes Barnard as saying he called it `` a Chinese कहावत, so कि लोगों होता लो it seriously. ''
जल्द बाद, the proverb होता become popularly attributed to Confucius.
The चर्चा of `` One चित्र लायक हजार शब्द '' बनाम `` एक Picture Worth टेन Thousand शब्द '' wan येन I hua और 10.000 मील worth 10.000 books is cited in सूचना graphics जहाँ the अवधारणा of many in अलग disciplines and संस्कृतियों.
a चित्र is worth a thousand शब्द
despite इस आधुनिक उत्पत्ति of the लोकप्रिय phrase, the भावना रै महरूम expressed by earlier लेखक.
For example the रूसी writer इवान Turgenev लिखा ( in fathers और बेटे in 1862 ), `` A चित्र shows me at a glance कया it takes दर्जनों of pages of a book to expound. ''
कंप्यूटर programmer और लेखक Fred Brooks makes an विपरीत statement regarding programming in the mythical man-month : `` Show me अपना flowcharts और conceal अपना टेबल, और i shall continue to be mystified.
दिखाएँ me अपना टेबल, और i won’t प्रायः need your flowcharts ; they’ll be स्पष्ट. ''
the phrase रै also been spoofed by जॉन McCarthy, the प्रसिद्ध computer वैज्ञानिक, to make the विपरीत पाइंट : `` as the Chinese कह, 1001 शब्द is लायक अधिक than a picture. ''
A ऋतु is a subdivision of the साल, चिह्नित by परिवर्तन in मौसम, ecology, and घंटों of daylight.
Seasons result इससे the वार्षिक revolution of the Earth around the Sun और the tilt of the धरती 's अक्ष सापेक्ष to the प्लेन of क्रान्ति.
in शीतोष्ण और polar regions, the सीज़न हैं चिह्नित by changes in the intensity of sunlight that पहुँच the Earth 's सतह, variations of which may cause पशु to go into शीतनिष्क्रियता or to migrate, and plants to be dormant.
During may, जून और जुलाई, the उत्तरी hemisphere is उजागर to अधिक direct धूप because the गोलार्ध faces the सूर्य.
The वही is true of the southern गोलार्ध in नवम्बर, दिसम्बर और जनवरी.
It is the tilt of the धरती कि causes the Sun to be उच्चतर in the sky during the गर्मियाँ महीने which increases the solar फ्लक्स.
however, due to मौसमी lag, जून, जुलाई और अगस्त are the hottest महीने in the northern गोलार्ध और दिसम्बर, जनवरी और फ़रवरी हैं the hottest महीने in the southern hemisphere.
In शीतोष्ण and subpolar regions, generally four पंचांग -आधारd seasons ( with उनके adjectives ) हैं पहचाना : वसन्त ( vernal ), summer ( estival ), पतझड़ ( autumnal ) and winter ( hibernal ).
however, ecologists ज़्यादातर उपयोग a छह season मॉडल लिये शीतोष्ण climate regions कि शामिल pre-spring ( prevernal ) and late summer ( serotinal ) as distinct सीज़न साथ with the traditional चार.
hot regions have two or तीन सीज़न ; the rainy ( or wet, or मानसून ) season और the शुष्क ऋतु, and in some तीव्र areas, a कूल or mild ऋतु.
in some भाग of the संसार, special `` seasons '' are loosely पारिभाषित आधारित on महत्वपूर्ण कार्यक्रम such as a hurricane season, बवंडर season or a wildfire season.
