डच निर्यात in 2006
At the time of writing the Netherlands is the 17th largest economy of the संसार.
( see : सूची of देशों by GDP ( nominal ) )
GDP प्रति capita is roughly $ 42,000 which puts it in the शीर्ष 10 of richest राष्ट्र in the world ( देखिए : सूची of देशों by जीडीपी ( PPP ) प्रति capita ).
Between 1996 and 2000 सालाना economic विकास ( जीडीपी ) averaged over 4 %, खूब above the European average.
विकास slowed considerably in 2001-05 as part of the वैश्विक आर्थिक slowdown.
2006 और 2007 however दिखाया economic growth of 3.4 % और 3.9 %.
the डच अर्थव्यवस्था थी hit considerably by the जारी वैश्विक वित्तीय crisis और the ensuing European कर्ज़ संकट.
अनेक बैंको गई bankrupt, और a क्रमांक of others था to प्राप्त सरकारी सहायता.
in 2009 the economy declined साथ 3.5 %, followed by दो years of mild विकास.
the डच economy is फिलहाल in a recession again, साथ an आर्थिक मनाही of 0.5 % in 2012.
महंगाई is at 3.2 % in फ़रवरी 2013.
Unemployment रै महरूम अपेक्षाकृत कम compared to other eu राष्ट्र for decades but after mid-2012 it रै देखी a तेज़ बढ़ाएँ और in February 2013 it has hit 7.7 %.
the Netherlands managed to maintain its aaa दरजा at तनिक जबतक कूच 2013 according to the three major credit rating एजेंसियों.

the America मीनार of the American General Center, the headquarters of बेकर ह्यूजेस

the कम्पनी is administered broadly in दो बांटती : the पूर्वी hemisphere with पाँच regions ( यूरोपीय, Africa, the मध्य ईस्ट, एशिया Pacific और russia/caspian ) and the western गोलार्ध with चार regions ( कनाडा, us जमीन, us गल्फ, and लैटिन America ).
प्रत्येक of these regions is subdivided into markets.
The संयुक्त राज्य one- cent सिक्का, commonly ज्ञात as a पैनी, is a ईकाई of करेंसी equaling one one-hundredth of a संयुक्त राज्य डालर.
The cent 's प्रतीक is ¢.
Its obverse has featured the प्रोफ़ाइल of अध्यक्ष अब्राहम lincoln चूंकि 1909, the centennial of उसके जनम.
From 1959 ( the sesquicentennial of Lincoln 's जनम ) to 2008, the रिवर्स featured the lincoln Memorial.
चार अलग reverse डिजाइन in 2009 सम्मानित Lincoln 's 200th birthday और a नई, स्थाई reverse – the संघ Shield – was introduced in 2010.
The coin is 0.75 इंच ( 19.05 mm ) in व्यास और 0.061 inches ( 1.55 mm ) in thickness.
The u.S. मिंट 's official नाम लिये a penny is `` '' and the U.S. Treasury 's आधिकारिक नाम is `` one cent टुकड़ा ''.
the colloquial पद पैनी derives इससे the British सिक्का of the वही name, the pre-decimal संस्करण of जिससे had a समान value.
in American English, कौड़ी is the plural form, other plural फ़ॉर्म पेंस और pee ( मानक उपयोग in अंग्रेजों English ) हैं नहीं used.
As of 2012, it costs the u.S. Mint 2.00 सेंट to make a cent because of the लागत of सामग्री and production.
This फिगर includes the mint’s fixed components for वितरण and fabrication, अनुमानित at $ 13 लाख in fy 2011.
It also शामिल मिंट overhead आबंटित to the penny, जिससे थी $ 17.7 लाख लिये 2011.
फिक्स्ड costs और ओवरहेड होता have to be अवशोषित by अन्य circulating coins बगैर the पैनी.
the घाटा in profitability due to producing the one cent सिक्का in the United States for the year of 2012 was $ 58,000,000.
इस थी a पतला decrease इससे 2011, the साल before, which था a उत्पादन घाटा of $ 60,200,000.

the एवोल्यूशन of पौधे रै resulted in increasing स्तर of जटिलता, इससे the earliest algal mats, through bryophytes, lycopods, ferns to the complex gymnosperms and angiosperms of आज.
जबकि many of the समूह जिससे appeared पहले continue to thrive, विशेषकर in the environments in which they विकसित, लिये a time प्रत्येक new ग्रेड of organisation became more `` successful '' than इसके predecessors.
in the ordovician period, around, the पहला जमीन पौधे appeared.
These began to diversify in the लेट सिल्यूरियन काल, around, और the परिणाम of उनके diversification are displayed in उल्लेखनीय विवरण in an जल्दी devonian चट्टान assemblage from the rhynie chert.
This chert preserved जल्दी plants in सेल्यूलर विवरण, petrified in volcanic स्रोतों.
by the middle of the Devonian काल, सबसे of the सुविधाएँ recognised in plants आज are present, including roots, leaves and द्वितीयक लकडी ; और, by लेट devonian टाइम्स, बीज had evolved.
लेट Devonian plants था thereby पहुँचे a degree of परिष्कार कि अनुमत उन्हें to रूप वनों of लम्बा trees.
Evolutionary नवीनता continued into the carboniferous काल and is स्टिल जारी today.
सबसे संयंत्र समूह were अपेक्षाकृत unscathed by the permo-triassic extinction इवेंट, हालांकि the structures of समुदायों changed.
इस may have नियत the scene लिये the रूप of the flowering पौधे in the Triassic ( ~ ), और their बाद diversification in the Cretaceous और Paleogene.
the नवीनतम प्रमुख group of plants to evolve यहूद the grasses, जिससे became महत्वपूर्ण in the mid-paleogene, इससे around.
the grasses, as well as अनेक अन्य groups, विकसित नई mechanisms of metabolism to जीवित the low और warm, dry शर्तें of the ऊष्णकटिबन्ध over the last.

assuming increased स्वीकृति, the मिलिंग industry होगा have to adapt to triticale, as the milling तकनीकों employed for wheat हैं unsuited to triticale.

a contingent fee ( in the United States ) or सशर्त शुल्क ( in इंग्लैण्ड and Wales ) is any शुल्क for सेवाएं provided where the fee is देय only if there is a favourable result.
in the law, it is defined as a `` fee charged for a lawyer 's सेवाएं only if the मुकदमा is successful or is favorably settled आउट of court....
Contingent fees हैं प्रायः गणना as a प्रतिशत of the क्लाएंट 's net रिकवरी. ''
In the अंग्रेज़ी legal system, it is generally referred to as no जीत no शुल्क.
A conditional शुल्क अनुबंध between a विधि firm और a client.
the usual रूप of इस अनुबंध is कि the solicitor होगा लो a विधि मामला on the समझना कि if lost, no payment is बना.
However, if the case is जीती, the वकील will be हकदार to the सामान्य शुल्क आधारित on hourly बिलिंग, plus a कामयाबी शुल्क.
the success fee in इंग्लैण्ड जरूर be as a percentage no greater than 100 % of the सामान्य fee.
इस contrasts with the आकस्मिकता शुल्क in the US, which देता the successful attorney a प्रतिशत of the damages awarded in एहसान of his क्लाएंट.
This makes it easier लिये the ग़रीब to pursue उनके civil rights since वरना, to sue किसी लिये a अपकृत्य, एक जरूर पहला be धनवान enough to pursue ऐसे litigation in the first place.
however, क्युकी of the ऊँची रिस्क, few attorneys will take मामले on a आकस्मिकता basis जबतक they महसूस the मामला रै good merit.
according to a 2004 किताब by विधि professor हर्बर्ट kritzer, contingent शुल्क were अनुमत as of कि साल in the following देशों : ऑस्ट्रेलिया, ब्राज़ील, कनाडा, the डोमिनिकन Republic, फ़्रांस, Greece, आयरलैंड, जापानी, नई Zealand, the United किंगडम और the संयुक्त राज्य.

recently, वे have been allowed in Belgium as well.

The Grímsvötn sub-glacial झीलों ( ; vötn = `` waters '', singular : ) और the ज्वालामुखी of the वही नाम हैं in South-East आइसलैंड.
वे हैं in the हाइलैंड्स of आइसलैंड at the northwestern पक्ष of the vatnajökull ice-cap.
The झीलों हैं at, at an उन्नयन of.
beneath the lakes is the magma chamber of the grímsvötn ज्वालामुखी.
grímsvötn is a basaltic ज्वालामुखी जिससे रै the उच्चतम फटना आवृत्ति of सब the volcanoes in Iceland और रै a southwest-northeast-trending फिशर system.
the विशाल climate-impacting laki फिशर फटना of 1783–1784 थी a भाग of the वही फिशर system.
Grímsvötn was erupting at the वही समय as laki दौरान 1783, लकिन जारी to erupt जबतक 1785.
Because सबसे of the ज्वालामुखी lies underneath vatnajökull, most of इसके eruptions have महरूम subglacial और the interaction of मैग्मा and meltwater from the ice causes phreatomagmatic explosive activity.
On 21 may 2011 at 19:25 utc, an फटना began, साथ high plumes accompanied by multiple भूकंप, resulting in cancellation of 900 फ़्लाइट in Iceland, and in the संयुक्त Kingdom, ग्रीनलैंड, जर्मनी, Ireland और नार्वे on 22–25 may.
Until 25 may the eruption scale था महरूम larger than कि of the 2010 फटना of eyjafjallajökull.
the eruption रोका at 02:40 utc on 25 May 2011, हालांकि there was कुछ विस्फोटक कार्यकलाप इससे the tephra vents affecting only the क्षेत्रफल around the crater.

A Permanent निवासी in कनाडा is a व्यक्ति जो is not a कनाडाई नागरिक but who रै महरूम granted permission to सजीव और कार्य in Canada बगैर any समय limit on his or उसके stay.
A permanent निवासी must सजीव in Canada लिये दो सालो out of प्रत्येक पाँच or रिस्क losing कि status.
A स्थाई Resident holds अनेक of the वही अधिकारों and responsibilities as a कनाडाई citizen, among others the सही to work for any एंटरप्राइज़ as well as लिये the federal or provincial सरकारी ( under प्रतिबंध of अभिगम अधिकारों to निश्चित regulated professions ).
the प्रमुख differences are कि निवासियों can नहीं :
vote in चुनावों in कनाडा ;

A graph of the US cpi from 1913 to 2006 ( in blue ), and its प्रतिशत annual change ( in रेड )
A उपभोक्ता दाम index ( cpi ) उपायों परिवर्तन in the दाम स्तर of a मार्केट basket of consumer goods और सेवाएं खरीदा by households.
The cpi in the संयुक्त States is defined by the Bureau of मजदूर आंकडे as `` a माप of the औसत बदलें over समय in the prices सशुल्क by शहरी consumers लिये a market बास्केट of consumer goods और सेवाएं. ''
the CPI is a सांख्यिकीय अनुमान constructed using the कीमतें of a नमूना of प्रतिनिधि items whose कीमतें हैं एकत्रित periodically.
Sub-indexes और sub-sub-indexes हैं computed लिये अलग categories और sub-categories of goods और सेवाएं, being संयुक्त to उपज the overall index with weights reflecting उनके shares in the कुल of the उपभोक्ता expenditures covered by the अनुक्रमणिका.
It is एक of अनेक दाम indices गणना by most नेशनल statistical एजेंसियों.
The annual प्रतिशत बदलें in a CPI is used as a माप of महंगाई.
a cpi can be used to अनुक्रमणिका ( i.e., समायोजन लिये the effect of inflation ) the real मान of मजदूरी, salaries, pensions, for regulating prices और लिये deflating monetary magnitudes to दिखाएँ परिवर्तन in रियल मान.
In most countries, the CPI is, along साथ the population जनसांख्यिकी and the USA National आय and उत्पाद खाते, one of the सबसे closely watched national economic statistics.
knocking on wood, or to टच लकडी, refers to the apotropaic tradition in पश्चिमी folklore of वस्तुतः touching/knocking on लकडी, or merely stating कि तुम हैं doing or intend same, in अनुक्रम to avoid `` tempting भाग्य `` बाद बनाना a favourable अवलोकन, a boast, or घोषणा concerning one 's own मौत.
रॉकर भुजा
Generally referred to भीतर the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of the आतंरिक combustion engine of automotive, marine, motorcycle and प्रत्यागमनी aviation इंजन, the rocker भुजा is an oscillating लीवर that conveys radial movement इससे the cam पालि into रैखिक movement at the poppet वाल्व to खोलें it.
एक end is raised and lowered by a घूर्णन पालि of the camshaft ( either directly or via a tappet ( lifter ) और pushrod ) while the other end acts on the वाल्व स्टेम.
When the camshaft lobe उठाता the बाहर of the भुजा, the अंदर दबाता bas on the valve स्टेम, opening the वाल्व.
जब the बाहर of the भुजा is permitted to return due to the camshafts rotation, the inside उदय, allowing the वाल्व वसन्त to close the वाल्व.
the ड्राइव कैम is चलित by the camshaft.
This pushes the rocker भुजा up और down परिचय the trunnion pin or rocker शाफ्ट.
घर्षण may be reduced at the पाइंट of contact with the वाल्व स्टेम by a रोलर कैम अनुसरणकर्ता.
a similar व्यवस्था हस्तांतरण the motion via another roller cam follower to a दूसरी rocker भुजा.
This rotates about the रॉकर shaft, और transfers the गति via a tappet to the poppet वाल्व.
in इस case इस opens the intake valve to the बेलन सिर.
the effective leverage of the arm ( और यूँ the फ़ोर्स it can exert on the वाल्व स्टेम ) is determined by the rocker भुजा अनुपात, the ratio of the अलहदा from the rocker भुजा 's center of रोटेशन to the tip divided by the अलहदा from the बीच of rotation to the पाइंट acted on by the camshaft or pushrod.
वर्तमान automotive डिज़ाइन favors रॉकर arm ratios of about 1.5:1 to 1.8:1.
However, in the past smaller धनात्मक ratios ( the वाल्व lift is greater than the कैम लिफ्ट ) और भी ऋणात्मक ratios ( वाल्व lift smaller than the कैम lift ) have महरूम प्रयुक्त.
अनेक pre-ww2 इंजन use 1:1 ( neutral ) ratios.
लिये car इंजन the रॉकर बाहें हैं generally steel stampings, providing a reasonable संतुलन of शक्ति, वज़न और किफायती cost.
क्युकी the रॉकर arms are, in भाग, reciprocating वज़न, excessive mass especially at the लीवर ends limits the इंजन 's क्षमता to reach high ऑपरेटिंग speeds.
`` the रात्रि the लाइट्स Went Out in जॉर्जिया '' is a दक्षिणी गोथिक सोंग written by songwriter Bobby रसेल और performed in 1972 by his then-wife vicki लॉरेंस.

In postal mail, a वापसी पता is an सुस्पष्ट inclusion of the पता of the व्यक्ति sending the संदेश.
it provides the recipient ( और sometimes प्राधिकृत intermediaries ) साथ a means to determine how to respond to the प्रेषक of the संदेश if needed.
the return address need not शामिल a प्रेषक 's नाम, लकिन should शामिल address or p.o. बक्सा details in the वही way as the delivery address should.
in some countries, the वापसी address is conventionally located in the अपर बाएँ हाथ कोने of the लिफाफा, कार्ड, or label.
In the संयुक्त किंगडम, the वापसी address is प्रायः लगाई on the reverse of the envelope, निकट the शीर्ष.
Businesses often उपयोग लिफाफे preprinted साथ a वापसी पता.
अनेक individuals have चादरें of चिपकने लेबल्स preprinted साथ उनके home पता to affix to उनके correspondence.
Charities sometimes शामिल ऐसे sheets in mailshots.
रोल्स of Return पता लेबल्स can be purchased from कंपनियाँ that sell personalized labels to provide individuals an easy रास्ता to छिलके और stick वापसी address लेबल्स to their लिफाफे.
the वापसी पता is नहीं required on डाक mail.
however, lack of a वापसी पता prevents the postal service from होने समर्थ to वापसी the item if it proves undeliverable ; such as इससे क्षति, postage due, or अमान्य गंतव्य.
ऐसे mail may यूँ become dead अक्षर मेल.
Should the return address be of a different state or देश, the mail may be routed through that स्थान लिये ease of return.
a nerve guidance conduit ( भी referred to as an कृत्रिम nerve conduit or artificial तंत्रिका graft, as opposed to an autograft ) is an कृत्रिम means of guiding axonal regrowth to facilitate तंत्रिका regeneration और is one of अनेक clinical उपचार लिये nerve चोटों.
When सीधा suturing of the two stumps of a severed तंत्रिका can नहीं be संपन्नता बगैर tension, the मानक नैदानिक उपचार for परिधीय तंत्रिका injuries is autologous तंत्रिका grafting.
Due to the सीमित availability of दाता tissue और functional रिकवरी in autologous तंत्रिका कलम, neural ऊतक अभियान्त्रिकी शोध has focused on the development of bioartificial nerve मार्गदर्शन conduits as an alternative उपचार, विशेषकर for large defects.
Similar तकनीकों हैं भी होने छान लिये nerve मरम्मत in the spinal cord लकिन nerve regeneration in the central बेचैन प्रणाली मुद्राएँ a वृहद challenge because इसके axons do not regenerate appreciably in उनके देशी पर्यावरण.
the creation of कृत्रिम conduits is भी ज्ञात as entubulation because the तंत्रिका ends and intervening गैप are enclosed भीतर a ट्यूब composed of biological or synthetic सामग्री.
Whether the conduit is in the form of a biologic ट्यूब, synthetic ट्यूब or tissue-engineered conduit, it should सुकर neurotropic और neurotrophic संचार between the proximal और distal ends of the nerve गैप, block बाह्य inhibitory कारकों, और provide a शारीरिक मार्गदर्शन लिये axonal regrowth.
The सबसे मौलिक उद्देश्य of a nerve guidance conduit is to combine शारीरिक, रासायनिक, और biological cues under conditions that होगा फोस्टर ऊतक formation.
सामग्री that have महरूम प्रयुक्त to मेक biologic tubes शामिल blood vessels और skeletal मांसपेशियां, जबकि nonabsorbable और bioabsorbable सिंथेटिक tubes have महरूम बना from silicone और polyglycolide respectively.
Tissue-engineered तंत्रिका मार्गदर्शन conduits are a संयोजन of अनेक तत्व : scaffold structure, scaffold सामग्री, सेल्यूलर therapies, neurotrophic factors and biomimetic सामग्री.
The choice of which physical, रासायनिक और biological cues to उपयोग is आधारित on the properties of the तंत्रिका पर्यावरण, which is नाजुक in बनाना the सबसे वांछनीय पर्यावरण लिये axon regeneration.
The factors कि कंट्रोल सामग्री चयन include biocompatibility, biodegradability, mechanical अखंडता, controllability दौरान तंत्रिका growth, implantation और sterilization.

Lodge फ्रीवे in डेट्रॉयट, Michigan.

Amoxicillin BP
amoxicillin ( इन ), formerly amoxycillin ( बैन ), और abbreviated amox, is a moderate-spectrum, bacteriolytic, β-lactam antibiotic used to दावत bacterial infections caused by susceptible microorganisms.
It is usually the ड्रग of चुनाव भीतर the class क्युकी it is बेहतर absorbed, following मौखिक प्रशासन, than अन्य β-lactam एंटीबायोटिक.
amoxicillin is one of the most आम एंटीबायोटिक prescribed लिये children.
The ड्रग became available in 1972.
Amoxicillin is susceptible to degradation by β-lactamase -producing जीवाणु, जिससे हैं resistant to a broad वर्णक्रम of β-lactam एंटीबायोटिक, such as पेनिसिलीन.
लिये इस कारण, it is often संयुक्त साथ clavulanic एसिड, a β-lactamase inhibitor.
इस increases प्रभावकारिता by reducing इसके susceptibility to β-lactamase resistance.
Lyndon Baines Johnson ( अगस्त 27, 1908 – January 22, 1973 ), प्रायः referred to as lbj, थी the 36th अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य ( 1963–1969 ), a position he assumed बाद his सेवा as the 37th वाइस अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य ( 1961–1963 ).
he is one of only four लोगों who परोसा in all four निर्वाचित संघीय offices of the संयुक्त States : प्रतिनिधि, Senator, Vice अध्यक्ष, और अध्यक्ष.
जॉनसन, a डेमोक्रेट from टेक्सास, परोसा as a संयुक्त States प्रतिनिधि इससे 1937–1949 और as a सीनेटर from 1949–1961, including छह सालो as संयुक्त राज्य सीनेट बहुमत नेता, दो as सीनेट अल्पसंख्यक Leader and two as सीनेट बहुमत Whip.
After campaigning unsuccessfully लिये the Democratic nomination in 1960, Johnson was asked by John F. कैनेडी to be उसके running mate लिये the 1960 अध्यक्षीय चुनाव.
Johnson succeeded to the प्रेसिडेंसी following the हत्या of John F. कैनेडी on नवम्बर 22, 1963, समाप्त Kennedy 's पद और was elected अध्यक्ष in उसके अपना right, winning by a विशाल margin over Barry Goldwater in the 1964 चुनाव.
Johnson थी greatly समर्थित by the लोकतांत्रिक Party और as अध्यक्ष, he थी जिम्मेदार for डिजाइनिंग the `` Great समाज `` विधान कि शामिल कानून कि upheld civil अधिकारों, पब्लिक प्रसारण, medicare, Medicaid, पर्यावरणीय protection, सहायता to शिक्षा, and his `` युद्ध on गरीबी. ''
जॉनसन थी प्रसिद्ध लिये उसके domineering personality and the `` जॉनसन treatment, '' his coercion of शक्तिशाली राजनेता in अनुक्रम to advance legislation.
meanwhile, जॉनसन escalated अमरीकी भागीदारी in the वियतनाम युद्ध, इससे 16,000 अमरीकी advisors/soldiers in 1963 to 550,000 combat सैनिकों in early 1968, as American हताहत soared और the सलाम process bogged bas.
the भागीदारी stimulated a विशाल एंग्री antiwar गति आधारित especially on university campuses in the u.S. and विदेश.
Summer दंगे broke आउट in सबसे प्रमुख शहरों after 1965, and अपराधों दरों soared, as his प्रतिद्वंद्वियों उठाया demands लिये `` law and order '' नीतियों.
the लोकतांत्रिक Party विभाजित in अनेक feuding गिरोहों, और after जॉनसन did poorly in the 1968 नई हैम्पशायर primary, he ended his बोली लिये reelection.
Republican रिचर्ड निक्सन थी elected to succeed उसे.
Historians argue कि Johnson 's presidency marked the शिखर of आधुनिक liberalism in the संयुक्त States बाद the New सौदे era.
जॉनसन is ranked favorably by some इतिहासकारों because of his घरेलू नीतियों.

The American sitcom The Big बंग सिद्धान्त, निर्मित और कार्यपालिका produced by Chuck lorre और विधेयक prady, premiered on सीबीएस on September 24, 2007.
The show centers on पाँच वर्ण : roommates Sheldon कूपर और लियोनार्ड hofstadter, two caltech physicists ; पैनी, a waitress और aspiring actress जो जीवनदान आरपार the हॉल ; और Leonard and शेल्डन 's मित्रों और co-workers aerospace इंजीनियर हावर्ड wolowitz, और astrophysicist राजेश Koothrappali.
Over समय, अनेक supporting वर्ण have महरूम promoted to starring roles : Leslie winkle ( ऋतु 1 recurring ; season 2 नियमित ; ऋतु 3 guest ), a physicist सहयोगी, और, at different टाइम्स, a प्रेमी of दोनो Leonard and हावर्ड ; Bernadette rostenkowski-wolowitz ( ऋतु 3 पुनरावर्ती ; ऋतु 4-present नियमित ), a microbiologist, हावर्ड 's fiancée और subsequent बीवी, और former part-time waitress alongside पैनी ; neuroscientist एमी Farrah fowler ( season 3 अतिथि ; ऋतु 4 पुनरावर्ती ; season 4-present regular ), जो joins the group after होने matched to Sheldon on a डेटिंग जालस्थल ; and comic book store-owner, Stuart खिलते ( सीज़न 2–5 पुनरावर्ती ; season 6-present नियमित ), जो replaces Howard as राज 's best dost when हावर्ड is in space.
The दिखाएँ भी सुविधाएँ numerous supporting वर्ण, प्रत्येक of जिसको plays a prominent भूमिका in a छोटी समूह of एपीसोड.
the अमरीकी Civil युद्ध ( acw ), also ज्ञात as the युद्ध between the राज्य or simply the Civil युद्ध ( see नामकरण ), was a सिविल युद्ध fought इससे 1861 to 1865 between the United राज्य ( the `` संघ '' or the `` उत्तर '' ) and several Southern slave राज्य कि घोषित their secession and formed the Confederate States of America ( the `` Confederacy '' or the `` South '' ).
The war had इसके origin in the समस्या of गुलामी, especially the एक्सटेंशन of गुलामी into the पश्चिमी territories.
Foreign powers did not intervene.
बाद four years of खूनी combat कि बाएँ over 600,000 सैनिको मुर्दे और नष्ट much of the South 's अवसंरचना, the confederacy collapsed, slavery was abolished, और the मुश्किल पुनर्निर्माण प्रक्रम of restoring नेशनल एकता और guaranteeing rights to the freed slaves began.
in the 1860 अध्यक्षीय election, Republicans, led by अब्राहम Lincoln, opposed expanding slavery into संयुक्त राज्य ' territories.
Lincoln won, लकिन पहले उसके inauguration on March 4, 1861, सात cotton-based slave states formed the confederacy.
outgoing Democratic President जेम्स Buchanan and the आवक Republicans अस्वीकृत secession as illegal.
Lincoln 's inaugural पता घोषित उसके प्रशासन होता not initiate civil war.
आठ बाकी स्लेव राज्य जारी to reject calls लिये secession.
confederate शक्तियां seized numerous federal forts भीतर territory claimed by the Confederacy.
a सलाम सम्मेलन failed to find a compromise, और दोनो पहलू prepared लिये war.
The confederates assumed that यूरोपीय देशों यहूद so dependent on `` किंग कपास `` कि वे होता intervene ; none किया and none पहचाना the new confederate States of अमेरिका.
hostilities began on April 12, 1861, जब confederate forces fired upon Fort Sumter, a कुंजी फोर्ट held by Union troops in दक्षिण Carolina.
lincoln called for प्रत्येक राज्य to provide सैनिकों to retake the fort ; नतीजतन, चार अधिक स्लेव states joined the Confederacy, bringing उनके कुल to eleven.
The संघ soon नियंत्रित the किनारा states and स्थापित a नवल blockade कि अबोध the दक्षिणी अर्थव्यवस्था.
the पूर्वी थिएटर थी inconclusive in 1861–62.
The autumn 1862 Confederate campaign into Maryland ( a Union राज्य ) ended साथ Confederate रिट्रीट at the बैटल of antietam, dissuading अंग्रेजों हस्तक्षेप.
lincoln issued the Emancipation Proclamation, which made ending गुलामी a युद्ध लक्ष्य.
to the west, by गर्मियाँ 1862 the संघ नष्ट the confederate नदी navy, then much of their western सेना, and the Union at Vicksburg split the confederacy in दो at the मिसिसिपी River.
in 1863, रॉबर्ट E. ली 's confederate incursion उत्तर ended at the बैटल of gettysburg.
पश्चिमी successes led to ulysses S. ग्रान्ट कमांड of all संघ सेना in 1864.
in the Western थिएटर, William T. शरमन drove ईस्ट to capture अटलांटा और marched to the समुद्र, destroying Confederate infrastructure साथ the way.
the संघ marshaled the resources और जनशक्ति to attack the confederacy इससे सब directions, and could afford to लड़ो battles of अपघर्षण through the Overland Campaign towards रिचमंड, the confederate पूंजी.
the defending Confederate फौज विफल, अग्रणी to Lee 's surrender to ग्रान्ट at appomattox अदालत हाउस on April 9, 1865.
The अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध थी एक of the earliest true औद्योगिक युद्धों.
Railroads, the टेलीग्राफ, steamships, और mass-produced हथियार यहूद employed extensively.

it remains the deadliest war in American इतिहास, resulting in the मौतों of an अनुमानित 750,000 soldiers और an undetermined क्रमांक of civilian casualties.
इतिहासकार जॉन Huddleston estimates the मौत toll at ten प्रतिशत of all Northern males 20–45 years old, and 30 percent of सब दक्षिणी श्वेत males aged 18–40.
Human एवोल्यूशन refers to the evolutionary process leading up to the appearance of modern humans.
जबकि it began साथ the last common ancestor of सब जीवन, the topic usually covers तभी the विकासवादी इतिहास of primates, in particular the genus Homo, and the emergence of होमो sapiens as a पृथक प्रजाति of hominids ( or `` ग्रेट apes '' ).
the पढ़ाई of इंसान evolution involves अनेक वैज्ञानिक disciplines, सहित शारीरिक anthropology, primatology, पुरातत्व, भाषाविज्ञान, विकासवादी मनोविज्ञान, embryology और आनुवंशिकी.
according to जेनेटिक studies, primates diverged from other स्तनधारियों परिचय in the Late Cretaceous period, and the earliest जीवाश्मों appear in the Paleocene, around.
The परिवार मानवनुमा diverged from the Hylobatidae ( गिबन ) family 15-20 लाख years ago, और around, the ponginae ( orangutans ), diverged from the मानवनुमा परिवार.
bipedalism is the basic adaption of the hominin लकीर, और the earliest bipedal Hominin is considered to be either sahelanthropus or orrorin, साथ Ardipithecus, a पूरा bipedal, coming somewhat later.
the गोरिल्ला और चिंपैंजी diverged around the वही time, about 4-6 लाख सालो पहले, और either Sahelanthropus or orrorin may be our पिछला shared पूर्वज with उन्हें.
The जल्दी bipedals आखिरकार evolved into the australopithecines and later the genus होमो.
The earliest documented सदस्यों of the genus होमो are होमो habilis which विकसित around ; the earliest species for which there is positive evidence of use of स्टोन टूल्स.
the brains of these जल्दी hominins यहूद परिचय the same size as कि of a chimpanzee.
During the अगला million सालो a प्रक्रम of encephalization began, और with the आगमन of होमो erectus in the चट्टान रिकार्ड, cranial क्षमता had doubled to 850 cm3.
होमो इरेक्टस और होमो ergaster were the first of the hominina to leave अफ़्रीकी, और these प्रजाति स्प्रेड through Africa, Asia, और यूरोपीय between.
It is believed that ये species यहूद the first to उपयोग fire and जटिल टूल्स.
according to the हाल अफ़्रीकी Ancestry theory, आधुनिक इंसानो evolved in अफ़्रीकी संभवतः इससे होमो heidelbergensis, होमो rhodesiensis or होमो antecessor और migrated out of the महाद्वीप कुछ 50,000 to 100,000 सालो पहले, replacing local populations of Homo इरेक्टस, होमो denisova, होमो floresiensis और होमो neanderthalensis.
Archaic Homo sapiens, the forerunner of anatomically आधुनिक इंसानो, विकसित between 400,000 और 250,000 सालो पहले.
हाल DNA evidence suggests कि several haplotypes of neanderthal उत्पत्ति are present among सब non-african populations, और neanderthals और अन्य hominids, ऐसे as Denisova hominin may have contributed up to 6 % of उनके genome to present-day humans. < संदर्भ name= '' 10.1126/science.1209202 '' > Anatomically modern humans विकसित इससे archaic Homo sapiens in the मध्य Paleolithic, परिचय 200,000 सालो ago.
The परिवर्तन to behavioral modernity with the development of सांकेतिक संस्कृति, language, और specialized lithic प्रौद्योगिकी happened around 50,000 सालो ago according to many विज्ञानियों although कुछ suggest a क्रमिक बदलें in बर्ताव over a longer समय स्पैन.

track and field is a sport comprising विभिन्न competitive एथलेटिक प्रतियोगिताओं based on running, jumping, and throwing.
the name of the खेल derives इससे the प्रतियोगिता स्थान : a स्टेडियम साथ an ओवल कार्यशील track around a ग्रास field.
the throwing और jumping कार्यक्रम generally take प्लेस in the सेंट्रल enclosed क्षेत्रफल.
Track and field falls अंतर्गत the छतरियाँ sport of एथलेटिक्स, जिससे also includes road कार्यशील, क्रॉस देश running, और race walking.
the two सबसे prestigious international track और फ़ील्ड प्रतियोगिताओं हैं held अंतर्गत the banner of athletics : the एथलेटिक्स प्रतियोगिता at the Olympic Games and the आइएएएफ World championships in Athletics.
the अंतरराष्ट्रीय संघ of एथलेटिक्स federations is the अंतरराष्ट्रीय शासी body लिये track and फ़ील्ड.
Track and फ़ील्ड events हैं generally individual खेल साथ एथलीट चुनौतीपूर्ण each अन्य to decide a single विक्टर.
The रेसिंग कार्यक्रम are won by the खिलाड़ी साथ the fastest समय, जबकि the कूद और फेंकना events हैं won by the खिलाड़ी who has हासिल the greatest अलहदा or height in the प्रतियोगिता.
the कार्यशील कार्यक्रम are categorised as sprints, middle and long-distance कार्यक्रम, relays, और hurdling.
Regular कूद कार्यक्रम include long jump, ट्रिपल jump, high जम्प and pole vault, while the सबसे आम throwing events हैं शॉट put, javelin, discus और हथौड़ा.
There हैं भी `` combined कार्यक्रम '', ऐसे as heptathlon और decathlon, in जिससे athletes compete in a number of the ऊपर events.
रिकॉर्ड हैं रखा of the बेहतरीन प्रदर्शन in विशिष्ट events, at संसार और नेशनल levels, सही down to a personal level.
However, if athletes हैं deemed to have violated the इवेंट 's rules or regulations, वे हैं disqualified इससे the प्रतियोगिता and उनके marks हैं erased.
In उत्तर अमेरिका, the पद track and फ़ील्ड may be प्रयुक्त to refer to एथलेटिक्स in सामान्य, बल्कि than specifically track और field कार्यक्रम.
The Gulf War ( 2 August 1990 – 28 फ़रवरी 1991 ), codenamed Operation Desert तूफ़ान ( 17 जनवरी 1991 – 28 February 1991 ) थी a war waged by a U.N.-authorized गठबन्धन force इससे 34 राष्ट्र led by the United राज्य, against इराकी in response to Iraq 's invasion और annexation of कुवैत.
The war is also ज्ञात under other names, ऐसे as the पारसी Gulf युद्ध, पहला गल्फ युद्ध, गल्फ युद्ध i, or the पहला इराकी War, before the term `` इराकी युद्ध '' became identified instead with the 2003 Iraq युद्ध ( भी referred to in the u.S. as `` Operation Iraqi स्वतंत्रता '' ).
Kuwait 's आक्रमण by इराकी सैनिकों कि began 2 अगस्त 1990 was मिले with अंतरराष्ट्रीय condemnation, और brought तात्कालिक economic प्रतिबंधों विरूद्ध Iraq by सदस्यों of the u.N. सुरक्षा परिषद.
u.S. अध्यक्ष George H. W. बुश deployed U.S. forces into सऊदी अरब, और urged other देशों to send their own शक्तियां to the scene.
An सरणी of राष्ट्र joined the Coalition.
the ग्रेट बहुमत of the गठबन्धन 's सैन्य शक्तियां were इससे the u.S., with सऊदी अरब, the संयुक्त Kingdom and मिश्र as leading योगदानकर्ता, in कि order.
सऊदी Arabia paid around us $ 36 billion of the US $ 60 अरब cost.
The युद्ध was चिह्नित by the beginning of सजीव न्यूज on the front lines of the लड़ो, with the primacy of the U.S. संजाल CNN.
the युद्ध रै भी earned the उपनाम वीडियो Game युद्ध बाद the रोज़ broadcast बिंब on फलक the U.S. bombers during Operation मरुस्थल तूफ़ान.
The initial विरोध to निकाल Iraqi सैनिकों इससे कुवैत began साथ an aerial बमबारी on 17 January 1991.
इस थी followed by a ground उत्पीड़न on 24 फ़रवरी.
इस थी a निर्णायक विजय लिये the गठबन्धन forces, जो liberated कुवैत और उन्नत into इराकी territory.
the गठबन्धन ceased their अग्रिम, and घोषित a cease-fire 100 घंटों after the मैदान अभियान started.
Aerial और मैदान कॉम्बैट was confined to इराकी, Kuwait, और क्षेत्रों on सऊदी Arabia 's किनारा.
इराकी launched scud missiles against गठबन्धन सैन्य targets in सऊदी Arabia and विरूद्ध Israel.
The nickel, in American usage, is a five- cent coin issued by the United States मिंट.
रचित of 75 % तांबे and 25 % nickel, the piece रै महरूम struck since 1866.
the चांदी half dime, equal to five सेंट, था महरूम issued since the 1790s.
The अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध caused आर्थिक hardship, driving gold और चांदी इससे circulation ; in जवाब, in प्लेस of low-value coins, the government at पहला issued पेपर करेंसी.
in 1865, Congress abolished the five-cent fractional करेंसी note after Spencer M. Clark, head of the करेंसी Bureau ( today the Bureau of नक्काशी और Printing ), placed उसके अपना portrait on the denomination.
बाद कामयाब परिचय of two-cent and three-cent pieces, without precious metal, Congress भी प्राधिकृत a five-cent टुकड़ा consisting of base मेटल ; the मिंट began striking this version in 1866.
the आरंभिक डिज़ाइन of the शील्ड nickel was struck until 1883, then replaced by the स्वतंत्रता Head nickel.
The Buffalo निकल थी introduced in 1913 as part of a drive to बढ़ाएँ the beauty of American coinage ; in 1938, the जेफरसन nickel followed.
in 2004 and 2005, खास डिजाइन in सम्मान of the bicentennial of the लुईस and Clark expedition were issued.
In 2006, the मिंट reverted to using जेफरसन निकल designer फेलिक्स Schlag 's असली रिवर्स ( or `` tails '' पक्ष ), हालांकि a नई obverse, by जेमी Franki, थी substituted.
As of 2013, it costs अधिक than ग्यारह सेंट to produce a nickel ; the मिंट is exploring the सम्भावना of reducing लागत by using less महंगी धातुओं.
a पोस्टर साथ पुष्प or clusters of flowers produced by बारह प्रजाति of flowering पौधे from different परिवारों
A flower, sometimes ज्ञात as a bloom or खिलना, is the reproductive ढांचा मिला in flowering plants ( पौधे of the प्रभाग magnoliophyta, also पुकारा angiosperms ).
the biological फलन of a पुष्प is to प्रभाव reproduction, usually by providing a यांत्रिकी लिये the union of शुक्राणु with अंडे.
पुष्प may सुकर outcrossing ( संलयन of शुक्राणु और eggs from अलग individuals in a population ) or allow selfing ( संलयन of sperm और अंडा from the वही पुष्प ).
कुछ पुष्प produce diaspores without fertilization ( parthenocarpy ).
Flowers contain sporangia and हैं the site जहाँ gametophytes develop.
पुष्प give rise to फल and seeds.
अनेक flowers have evolved to be आकर्षक to animals, so as to cause उन्हें to be सदिश for the transfer of पराग.
In addition to facilitating the जनन of flowering पौधे, पुष्प have long महरूम admired और used by इंसानो to beautify their environment, and भी as वस्तुएँ of रोमांस, ritual, धर्म, आयुर्विज्ञान and as a source of खाना.
the McDonnell डगलस ( अभी बोइंग ) F-15 Eagle is a twin-engine, all-weather रणनीतिक fighter designed by McDonnell Douglas to लाभ और maintain air बड़प्पन in aerial combat.
it is माना among the सबसे कामयाब आधुनिक सेनानी, साथ over 100 aerial कॉम्बैट victories साथ no losses in dogfights.
Following reviews of proposals, the United States एयर फ़ोर्स selected mcdonnell डगलस ' डिज़ाइन in 1967 to meet the service 's need लिये a dedicated एयर बड़प्पन सेनानी.
the Eagle first उड़ाया in जुलाई 1972, और डाला सेवा in 1976.
चूंकि the 1970s, the त्रिभुज रै महरूम exported to इसराईल, Japan, सऊदी Arabia, और अन्य राष्ट्र.
the f-15 was originally envisioned as a pure एयर superiority वायुयान.
इसके डिज़ाइन शामिल a secondary ground-attack काबिलियत कि was largely अप्रयुक्त.
The डिज़ाइन proved लचीली पर्याप्त कि an all-weather स्ट्राइक डेरिवेटिव, the F-15E स्ट्राइक त्रिभुज, was later developed, and डाला सेवा in 1989.
The F-15 त्रिभुज is expected to be in सेवा साथ the U.S. Air फ़ोर्स past 2025.
Mimio is a ब्रांड name of a line of प्रौद्योगिकी products aimed at the शिक्षा मार्केट.
The primary products are केन्द्रित around computer whiteboard इंटरैक्टिव शिक्षण डिवाइस.
MimioCapture devices भी allow उपयोक्ता to कैप्चर all of the ink strokes कि हैं लिखा on the whiteboard.
When used in संयोजन साथ a video प्रोजेक्टर it turns the ordinary whiteboard surface into a fully interactive whiteboard.
The product line was originally designed by Virtual Ink.
on अक्तूबर 4, 2006 newell rubbermaid acquired the Mimio इंटरैक्टिव whiteboard ( iWB ) उत्पाद line.
rahab of जेरिको
rahab, ( ; ; ) was, according to the किताब of Joshua, a स्त्री who lived in जेरिको in the Promised Land और assisted the israelites in capturing the नगर.

The संगठन of American States ( स्पेनी : organización de लॉस estados americanos, Portuguese : Organização डॉस estados americanos, French : संगठन देस états américains ), or the oas, is a क्षेत्रीय अंतरराष्ट्रीय संगठन.
The oas थी founded on 30 April 1948, और has its headquarters in वॉशिंगटन, d.C., संयुक्त States.
इसके members are the 35 independent राज्य of the americas.
चूंकि 26 May 2005, the सचिव सामान्य of oas रै महरूम जोस मिगुएल Insulza.
क्रिस्टोफर कोलंबस ( इतालवी : Cristoforo Colombo ; स्पेनी : cristóbal colón ; पुर्तगाली : cristóvão कोलोन ; पहले 31 अक्तूबर 145120 May 1506 ) थी an इतालवी explorer, navigator, और colonizer, born in the गणतंत्र of Genoa, in कया is आज northwestern Italy.
अंतर्गत the auspices of the Catholic monarchs of स्पेन, he completed four voyages across the अटलांटिक समंदर कि led to सामान्य European जागरूकता of the American continents.
those voyages, and his efforts to स्थापित स्थाई settlements on the island of हिस्पानिओला, initiated the स्पेनी colonization of the नई World.
In the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of उभरते पश्चिमी साम्राज्यवाद और आर्थिक प्रतियोगिता between यूरोपीय kingdoms seeking माल through the establishment of व्यापार routes और colonies, Columbus 's speculative प्रस्ताव, to पहुँचें the ईस्ट इंडीज by sailing westward, आखिरकार received the support of the स्पेनी क्राउन, जिससे देखी in it a promise, however रिमोट, of gaining the अपर हाथ over rival powers in the प्रतियोगिता लिये the lucrative मसाला व्यापार साथ एशिया.
दौरान his पहला voyage in 1492, instead of reaching जापानी as he था intended, कोलंबस उतरा in the Bahamas archipelago, at a locale he named सैन Salvador.
over the कोर्स of तीन अधिक voyages, Columbus visited the वृहद और lesser Antilles, as खूब as the caribbean coast of वेनेजुएला and सेंट्रल अमेरिका, claiming उन्हें for the स्पेनी साम्राज्य.
हालांकि कोलंबस was नहीं the पहला यूरोपीय एक्सप्लोरर to reach the Americas ( having महरूम preceded by the नॉर्स expedition led by leif Ericson in the 11th सदी ), कोलंबस 's voyages led to the पहला स्थायी यूरोपीय contact साथ the Americas, inaugurating a काल of यूरोपीय खोजी, conquest, and colonization कि lasted लिये अनेक centuries.
They था, therefore, an enormous प्रभाव in the historical development of the आधुनिक Western world.
कोलंबस himself देखी his accomplishments primarily in the लाइट of the spreading of the ईसाई religion.
never admitting कि he had पहुँचे a महाद्वीप previously अनजान to Europeans, बल्कि than the ईस्ट इंडीज he had नियत आउट लिये, कोलंबस पुकारा the निवासियों of the lands he visited indios ( Spanish लिये `` Indians `` ).
कोलंबस 's strained संबंध with the Spanish crown और its नियुक्त औपनिवेशिक administrators in अमेरिका led to his गिरफ़्तार और dismissal as governor of the settlements on the द्वीप of Hispaniola in 1500, और बाद to protracted litigation over the लाभ जिससे कोलंबस और उसके वारिस claimed यहूद owed to them by the crown.
करवाया in Germany, the boxer is a breed of stocky, medium-sized, short-haired कुत्तो.
The कोट is चिकना and tight-fitting ; colors हैं fawn or brindled, साथ or without white markings, which may cover the entire body.
Boxers are brachycephalic ( वे have broad, short skulls ), and have a वर्गाकार muzzle, mandibular prognathism ( an underbite ), very strong jaws, और a शक्तिशाली bite ideal लिये hanging on to विशाल prey.

सीरियल ata ( sata ) is a कंप्यूटर बस इंटरफ़ेस that connects host बस adapters to द्रव्यमान भंडार डिवाइस ऐसे as hard disk drives और ऑप्टिकल drives.
सीरियल ata replaces the पुरानी at Attachment मानक ( ata ; बाद referred to as समानांतर ata or PATA ), offering several लाभ over the पुरानी interface : घटाया केबल size और लागत ( सात conductors बजाय of 40 ), native hot swapping, तेज़ आंकड़ा ट्रांसफ़र through उच्चतर signalling दरों, और more efficient ट्रांसफ़र through an ( वैकल्पिक ) I/O queuing प्रोटोकॉल.
sata host adapters and डिवाइस communicate via a high-speed serial cable over two pairs of conductors.
in कंट्रास्ट, parallel ata ( the redesignation लिये the legacy ata specifications ) प्रयुक्त a 16-bit चौड़ी आंकड़ा bus साथ अनेक अतिरिक्त support and कंट्रोल सिग्नल, all ऑपरेटिंग at much निम्नतर frequency.
To ensure backward संगतता साथ विरासत ata तन्त्र और applications, sata उपयोग the same basic ata and atapi command-set as legacy ata डिवाइस.
SATA has replaced समानांतर ata in उपभोक्ता desktop और laptop कंप्यूटर, और रै largely replaced PATA in नई अंतःस्थापित applications.
SATA 's मार्केट share in the desktop PC मार्केट थी 99 % in 2008.
PATA remains widely प्रयुक्त in औद्योगिक and अंतःस्थापित अनुप्रयोग कि use compactflash भंडार, भी though the नई CFast standard is आधारित on SATA.
सीरियल ata industry compatibility विशेषताएँ originate from the सीरियल ATA अंतरराष्ट्रीय संगठन ( उर्फ.
SATA-IO, serialata.org ).
the SATA-IO group collaboratively creates, reviews, ratifies, और publishes the interoperability विशेषताएँ, the test cases, and plug-fests.
as with अनेक अन्य industry संगतता मानकों, the SATA content स्वामित्व is transferred to अन्य उद्योग bodies : primarily the incits t13 subcommittee ata, the incits T10 उपसमिति ( scsi ) ; a subgroup of t10 जिम्मेदार लिये Serial संलग्न SCSI ( SAS ).
the complete specification इससे sata-io.
the remainder of this article होगा try to use the terminology and विशेषताएँ of sata-io.
the इतिहास of the अंतरजाल began with the development of इलेक्ट्रॉनिक computers in the 1950s.
the पब्लिक was first introduced to the concepts कि होता lead to the अंतरजाल when a संदेश थी sent over the ARPANet इससे computer science प्राध्यापक Leonard Kleinrock 's प्रयोगशाला at विश्वविद्यालयों of California, लॉस एंजिल्स ( ucla ), after the दूसरी टुकड़ा of संजाल equipment थी संस्थापित at Stanford शोध संस्थान ( श्री ).
Packet switched संजाल ऐसे as ARPANET, Mark i at NPL in the uk, cyclades, Merit संजाल, Tymnet, and telenet, were विकसित in the लेट 1960s and early 1970s using a किस्में of प्रोटोकॉल.
the arpanet in particular led to the विकास of प्रोटोकॉल for internetworking, in which अनेक पृथक networks could be joined together into a संजाल of networks.
in 1982, the अंतरजाल protocol सुइट ( TCP/IP ) थी मानकीकृत, and नतीजतन, the अवधारणा of a world-wide संजाल of interconnected TCP/IP संजाल, पुकारा the अंतरजाल, थी introduced.
Access to the ARPANET was विस्तारित in 1981 जब the नेशनल Science न्यास ( NSF ) विकसित the Computer विज्ञान Network ( csnet ) and again in 1986 when nsfnet provided अभिगम to supercomputer साइट in the United States इससे शोध और शिक्षा संगठन.
Commercial अंतरजाल सेवा providers ( isps ) began to emerge in the लेट 1980s और early 1990s.
the ARPANET थी decommissioned in 1990.
The अंतरजाल was commercialized in 1995 जब nsfnet थी decommissioned, removing the पिछला restrictions on the उपयोग of the अंतरजाल to carry वाणिज्यिक traffic.
Since the mid-1990s, the Internet रै था a क्रांतिकारी प्रभाव on culture और कॉमर्स, सहित the वृद्धि of near-instant संचार by इलेक्ट्रॉनिक मेल, तत्काल messaging, आवाज़ over अंतरजाल प्रोटोकॉल ( VoIP ) `` फोन काल्स '', two-way interactive वीडियो काल्स, and the संसार चौड़ी Web साथ इसके चर्चा forums, ब्लॉग, सोशल नेटवर्किंग, और online shopping साइट.
The research and education जातियाँ continues to develop and use उन्नत संजाल ऐसे as nsf 's बहुत ऊँची speed Backbone Network सेवा ( vBNS ), internet2, और National LambdaRail.
increasing amounts of data हैं transmitted at उच्चतर and उच्चतर speeds over fiber optic networks operating at 1-gbit/s, 10-gbit/s, or more.
The अंतरजाल 's कब्ज़ा over the वैश्विक संचार लैंडस्केप was लगभग instant in historical शर्तें : it तभी communicated 1 % of the information बहती through two-way दूरसंचार networks in the साल 1993, already 51 % by 2000, और more than 97 % of the telecommunicated सूचना by 2007.
आज the Internet continues to grow, driven by कभी वृहद amounts of online information, कॉमर्स, entertainment, and social नेटवर्किंग.

Calcitonin ( भी known as thyrocalcitonin ) is a 32-amino एसिड रैखिक polypeptide hormone that is produced in humans primarily by the parafollicular cells ( also known as C-cells ) of the थायराइड, और in अनेक अन्य पशु in the ultimobranchial देह.
it अधिनियमों to reduce रक्त कैल्सियम ( ca2+ ), opposing the प्रभाव of parathyroid hormone ( pth ).
calcitonin रै been मिला in मछली, reptiles, पक्षियों, और mammals.
इसके importance in humans रै नहीं महरूम as खूब स्थापित as इसके महत्व in other animals, as इसके function is usually not significant in the regulation of normal कैल्सियम समस्थापन.
it belongs to calcitonin-like protein परिवार.

The मूक majority is an unspecified विशाल majority of लोगों in a country or group जो do not express their राय publicly.
the term थी popularized ( though नहीं first प्रयुक्त ) by U.S. अध्यक्ष Richard Nixon in a November 3, 1969, speech in जिससे he कहा, `` और so tonight—to तुम, the ग्रेट silent बहुमत of my fellow americans—i ask लिये अपना support. ''
in this उपयोग it referred to those Americans who किया नहीं join in the विशाल demonstrations विरूद्ध the Vietnam War at the time, who did नहीं join in the counterculture, और who किया not participate in पब्लिक प्रवचन.
निक्सन साथ साथ अनेक अन्य saw this समूह of मध्य अमेरिकी as होने overshadowed in the मीडिया by the अधिक vocal अल्पसंख्यक.
The phrase थी प्रयुक्त in the 19th सदी as a euphemism referring to सब the लोगों who have died, and others have प्रयुक्त it पहले और बाद निक्सन to refer to समूह of मतदाता in various राष्ट्र of the संसार.

रेड ( अनावश्यक सरणी of independent डिस्क, originally अनावश्यक सरणी of inexpensive डिस्क ) is a भंडार technology कि combines multiple डिस्क drive components into a लॉजिकल ईकाई.
Data is distributed आरपार the drives in one of अनेक तरीके called `` रेड स्तर '', depending on the level of redundancy और performance required.
the पद `` रेड '' थी first defined by दाउद Patterson, Garth A. Gibson, और रैंडी Katz at the विश्वविद्यालयों of California, Berkeley in 1987.
Marketers representing industry रेड निर्माताओं बाद attempted to reinvent the पद to describe a अनावश्यक सरणी of independent डिस्क as a means of disassociating a low-cost अपेक्षा from RAID प्रौद्योगिकी.
रेड is अभी used as an umbrella term लिये कंप्यूटर आंकड़ा storage schemes कि can divide and replicate data among अनेक शारीरिक ड्राइव : रेड is an example of storage virtualization और the array can be accessed by the operating system as one सिंगल drive.
the different schemes or architectures हैं named by the word RAID followed by a क्रमांक ( e.g. RAID 0, RAID 1 ).
प्रत्येक scheme provides a अलग संतुलन between the कुंजी लक्ष्य : विश्वसनीयता और availability, प्रदर्शन और क्षमता.
RAID स्तर वृहद than रेड 0 provide protection विरूद्ध unrecoverable ( सेक्टर ) read त्रुटियाँ, as खूब as whole डिस्क विफलता.
A lymphocyte is a प्रकार of white रक्त कोशिका in the vertebrate immune system.
अंतर्गत the सूक्ष्मदर्शी, lymphocytes can be divided into large lymphocytes और small lymphocytes.
विशाल granular lymphocytes शामिल प्राकृतिक killer cells ( nk कोशिकाएं ).
छोटी lymphocytes consist of T cells and b कोशिकाएं.

grits refers to a ground-corn खाना of Native अमरीकी उत्पत्ति, that is आम in the Southern United राज्य and मुख्यतः eaten at नाश्ता.
आधुनिक grits are commonly made of alkali-treated मकई known as hominy.
Grits हैं समान to other मोटा maize-based porridges इससे around the संसार ऐसे as polenta or the thinner farina.
`` तत्काल grits '' have been processed to गति कुकिंग.
the word `` grits '' गर्भाशयी from the बूढ़ा अंग्रेज़ी word `` grytt, '' अर्थ coarse भोजन.

sometimes, grits are पुकारा sofkee or sofkey ( इससे a देशी अमरीकी muskogee word ).
In आणविक biology, इंसान chorionic gonadotropin ( hcg ) is a हार्मोन produced by the निषेचित अंडा after conception.
बाद दौरान pregnancy it is बना by the developing placenta, और बाद by the placental घटक syncytiotrophoblast.
Some cancerous tumors उपज इस हार्मोन ; इसलिए, elevated स्तर measured जब the रोगी is नहीं गर्भवती can सीसे to a कर्कट निदान.
however, it is नहीं ज्ञात whether इस उत्पादन is a contributing cause or an effect of tumorigenesis.

Coca-Cola is a carbonated नरम drink बेची in stores, रेस्तरां, और vending मशीने in every देश except क्यूबा और North कोरियाई.
it is produced by the coca-cola कम्पनी of Atlanta, जॉर्जिया, और is प्रायः referred to simply as कोक ( a registered ट्रेडमार्क of the coca-cola कम्पनी in the संयुक्त States since कूच 27, 1944 ).
Originally intended as a पेटेंट medicine जब it थी invented in the लेट 19th सदी by जॉन Pemberton, Coca-Cola was खरीदा आउट by बिजनेसमैन Asa griggs Candler, whose marketing tactics led Coke to its dominance of the संसार soft-drink market throughout the 20th सदी.
The company produces concentrate, जिससे is तब बेची to licensed Coca-Cola bottlers throughout the संसार.
The bottlers, जो थाम territorially विशेष अनुबंध साथ the कम्पनी, produce समाप्त उत्पाद in डिब्बे और बोतलों from the concentrate in combination साथ filtered water और sweeteners.
the bottlers then बेचें, वितरित और merchandise coca-cola to retail स्टोर्स and वेंडिंग machines.
Such bottlers include Coca-Cola Enterprises, जिससे is the largest सिंगल Coca-Cola bottler in उत्तर अमेरिका और पश्चिमी यूरोपीय.
The coca-cola कम्पनी भी बिकता concentrate लिये सोडा स्रोतों to major रेस्तरां और खाना सेवा distributors.
The coca-cola कम्पनी has, on occasion, introduced अन्य cola पेय अंतर्गत the कोक ब्रांड name.
The सबसे common of ये is Diet Coke, with others including caffeine-free Coca-Cola, Diet कोक caffeine-free, Coca-Cola चेरी, Coca-Cola Zero, coca-cola वैनिला, और special संस्करण with lemon, lime or कॉफी.
Based on Interbrand 's best global ब्रांड 2011, Coca-Cola थी the संसार 's most मूल्यवान ब्रांड.
An ombudsman is an आधिकारिक, usually appointed by the government or by parliament लकिन with a significant degree of स्वतंत्रता, जो is चार्ज with representing the रूचि of the public by investigating और संबोधित complaints of maladministration or उल्लंघन of अधिकारों.
In some देशों an इंस्पेक्टर सामान्य, नागरिक एडवोकेट or अन्य आधिकारिक may have कर्तव्य समान to those of a national ombudsman, और may also be नियुक्त by the विधानमंडल.
नीचे the नेशनल स्तर an ombudsman may be नियुक्त by a state, लोकल or नगरपालिका government, and unofficial ombudsmen may be appointed by, or भी work लिये, a corporation ऐसे as a utility प्रदायक or a समाचारपत्र, लिये an ngo, or लिये a professional नियामक body.
whether नियुक्त by the विधानमंडल, the executive, or an organization ( or, less अक्सर, निर्वाचित by the constituency कि he or she serves ), the typical कर्तव्य of an ombudsman हैं to investigate शिकायत and attempt to निराकरण उन्हें, प्रायः through सुझाव ( बाइंडिंग or नहीं ) or मध्यस्थता.
ombudsmen sometimes भी उद्देश्य to identify systemic मुद्दे अग्रणी to poor service or breaches of people 's rights.
at the नेशनल level, सबसे ombudsmen have a चौड़ी जनादेश to deal with the entire पब्लिक सेक्टर, और sometimes also elements of the private sector ( लिये उदाहरण, contracted service providers ).
In कुछ मामले, there is a more restricted जनादेश, for example साथ particular सेक्टर of society.
More हाल developments have शामिल the creation of specialised Children 's ombudsman और सूचना Commissioner एजेंसियों.
in some jurisdictions an ombudsman चार्ज साथ the handling of चिंताएं about नेशनल सरकारी is अधिक formally referred to as the `` Parliamentary कमिश्नर '' ( e.g. the United Kingdom संसदीय Commissioner लिये प्रशासन, and the Western ऑस्ट्रेलियाई राज्य ombudsman ).
In many देशों जहाँ the ombudsman 's remit extends परे dealing साथ कथित maladministration to promoting और protecting इंसान अधिकारों, the ombudsman is recognised as the national इंसान अधिकारों संस्था.
the post of ombudsman था by the समाप्त of the 20th century महरूम instituted by सबसे governments and by कुछ intergovernmental organizations such as the European Union.
Making a complaint to an ombudsman is प्रायः free of charge.

New इंग्लैण्ड is a प्रदेश in the northeastern कोने of the संयुक्त States consisting of the छह राज्य of maine, नई हैम्पशायर, वर्मांट, मैसाचुसेट्स, rhode Island, और कनेक्टिकट.
नई इंग्लैण्ड is bordered by नई यॉर्क राज्य to the southwest, Quebec to the northwest, और नई Brunswick and the अटलांटिक समंदर to the ईस्ट.
in one of the earliest अंग्रेज़ी settlements in North अमेरिका, Pilgrims इससे इंग्लैण्ड first settled in नई इंग्लैण्ड in 1620, to रूप plymouth Colony.
टेन years बाद, the Puritans settled north of plymouth Colony in बोस्टन, thus forming मैसाचुसेट्स Bay उपनिवेश.
Over the next 130 years, New England लड़ा in चार फ्रेंच और भारतीय Wars, जबतक the अंग्रेजों defeated the फ्रेंच और उनके देशी allies in North अमेरिका.
in the late 18th सदी, the नई इंग्लैण्ड colonies initiated the प्रतिरोध to the British पार्लियामेंट 's efforts to impose नई taxes बगैर the consent of the colonists.
the Boston चाय पार्टी was a विरोध to which Great ब्रिटेन responded साथ a श्रेणी of punitive कानून stripping मैसाचुसेट्स of self-government, जिससे were termed the `` Intolerable Acts `` by the colonists.
The confrontation led to खोलें warfare in 1775, the expulsion of the अंग्रेजों authorities from नई इंग्लैण्ड in spring 1776, और the घोषणा of स्वतंत्रता in जुलाई 1776.
कुछ of the पहला आंदोलनों of अमरीकी literature, philosophy, and education originated in नई England.
the region played a prominent भूमिका in the गति to abolish गुलामी, और was the पहला प्रदेश of the संयुक्त राज्य to be रूपांतरित by the औद्योगिक क्रान्ति.
आज, नई England is a प्रमुख संसार center of शिक्षा, ऊँची प्रौद्योगिकी, बीमे, and आयुर्विज्ञान.
बोस्टन is इसके सांस्कृतिक, वित्तीय, शैक्षणिक, चिकित्सा और transportation बीच.
प्रत्येक state is principally subdivided into small incorporated municipalities ज्ञात as नई England कस्बों, जिससे हैं प्रायः governed by town बैठक.
the तभी unincorporated territory in नई इंग्लैण्ड exists in the sparse, उत्तरी regions of वर्मांट, New हैम्पशायर, और maine.
चूंकि 1970, voters have more often समर्थित liberal candidates at the राज्य and federal स्तर than those of any अन्य region in the संयुक्त राज्य.
नई इंग्लैण्ड is the only एक of the संयुक्त राज्य Census Bureau 's नौ क्षेत्रीय divisions जिनकी name करता नहीं derive इससे इसके भूगोल, और it is the only multi-state region साथ clear, सतत सीमाएँ.
it maintains a दमदार भाव of cultural identity set apart इससे the बाकी of the country, हालांकि the शर्तें of this identity are प्रायः लडे, combining puritanism साथ liberalism, agrarian जीवन with उद्योग, and isolation साथ आव्रजन.

the पूर्वी Time मण्डल ( ET ) encompasses 17 u.S. राज्य in the eastern भाग of the संलग्न संयुक्त राज्य, parts of कनाडा और three countries in South America.
स्थान that उपयोग पूर्वी मानक समय ( est ) जब observing मानक time ( autumn/winter ) हैं 5 hours पीछे Coordinated सार्वभौमिक समय ( ).
Eastern daylight Time ( edt ), जब observing daylight saving समय ( spring/summer ) is 4 घंटों पीछे Coordinated सार्वभौमिक समय ( ).
in the northern भाग of the समय zone, दौरान the दूसरी संडे in कूच, at 2:00 a.m. est, clocks हैं उन्नत to 3:00 a.m. EDT leaving a एक घंटा `` gap. ''
दौरान the first संडे in नवम्बर, at 2:00 a.m. EDT, clocks are स्थानांतरित back to 1:00 a.m. EST, यूँ `` duplicating '' एक hour.
दक्षिणी भाग of the मण्डल ( पनामा और the Caribbean ) do नहीं observe daylight saving.
मानक रूप of the periodic table.
The colors represent अलग categories of तत्व explained नीचे.
the periodic तालिका is a tabular प्रदर्शक of the chemical elements, व्यवस्थित on the आधार of उनके परमाणु संख्याएँ, electron configurations, और पुनरावर्ती रासायनिक properties.
Elements हैं प्रस्तुत in order of increasing atomic क्रमांक ( number of protons ).
the मानक form of तालिका comprises an 18 × 7 ग्रिड or main body of elements, positioned above a छोटी double पंक्ति of elements.
the table can also be deconstructed into चार rectangular ब्लॉक : the s-block to the बाएँ, the p-block to the सही, the d-block in the middle, and the f-block नीचे कि.
the पंक्ति of the तालिका are called अवधि ; the कालम of the s-, d-, और p-blocks हैं called समूह, साथ कुछ of ये having names ऐसे as the हैलोजन्स or the प्रतिष्ठित गैसों.
चूंकि, by परिभाषा, a आवधिक तालिका incorporates पुनरावर्ती रुझान, any such table can be used to derive संबंध between the गुण of the elements और भविष्यवाणी the गुण of नई, yet to be discovered or synthesized, तत्व.
as a result, a periodic table—whether in the मानक रूप or some other variant—provides a उपयोगी framework for analyzing रासायनिक बर्ताव, और ऐसे tables हैं widely प्रयुक्त in chemistry and अन्य sciences.
Although precursors exist, Dmitri Mendeleev is generally credited साथ the publication, in 1869, of the पहला widely पहचाना आवधिक तालिका.
he developed his तालिका to illustrate आवधिक trends in the गुण of the then-known तत्व.
Mendeleev also predicted कुछ properties of then-unknown elements कि होता be अपेक्षित to fill gaps in इस तालिका.
सबसे of his पूर्वानुमान यहूद proved सही जब the तत्व in question were subsequently खोजा.
mendeleev 's आवधिक table रै चूंकि been expanded और परिष्कृत with the डिस्कवरी or संश्लेषण of further नई elements और the development of नई सैद्धांतिक models to explain रासायनिक बर्ताव.
सब elements इससे परमाणु संख्याएँ 1 ( हाइड्रोजन ) to 118 ( ununoctium ) have महरूम discovered or synthesized.
the तत्व इससे 1 to 98 ( californium ) have महरूम मिला to मौजूद naturally, हालांकि some are found only in ट्रेस amounts and यहूद initially खोजा by संश्लेषण in laboratories.
The तत्व बाद 98 have only been synthesized in laboratories.
उत्पादन of तत्व beyond ununoctium is being pursued, साथ the सवाल of how the आवधिक तालिका may need to be परिवर्धित to accommodate any ऐसे परिवर्धन होने a पदार्थ of जारी बहस.
numerous सिंथेटिक radionuclides of naturally occurring elements have भी महरूम उत्पादित in laboratories.
minecraft is a सैंडबॉक्स इंडी खेल originally created by स्वीडिश प्रोग्रामर markus `` पायदान '' persson और बाद विकसित and प्रकाशित by mojang.
It was publicly released लिये the PC on May 17, 2009, as a developmental अल्फा version और, after gradual updates, was प्रकाशित as a full release संस्करण on November 18, 2011.
a संस्करण for एंड्रॉइड थी released a माह earlier on October 7, और an आईओएस version थी released on November 17, 2011.
on may 9, 2012, the game थी released on Xbox 360 as an एक्सबॉक्स सजीव आर्केड खेल, co-developed by 4j studios.
All versions of Minecraft प्राप्त आवधिक अद्यतन.
the creative and भवन पहलुओं of Minecraft allow players to निर्माण constructions out of textured घन in a 3D procedurally generated world.
अन्य activities in the खेल शामिल खोजी, gathering संसाधन, crafting and combat.
Gameplay in इसके वाणिज्यिक रिलीज has दो प्रिंसिपल modes : survival, जिससे requires players to acquire संसाधन और maintain their स्वास्थ्य and भूख ; और creative, जहाँ खिलाड़ी have an unlimited supply of resources, the क्षमता to fly, and no health or hunger.
A तीसरा gameplay विधि named hardcore is the same as अस्तित्व, differing only in परेशानी ; it is नियत to hardest setting और respawning is disabled, forcing खिलाड़ी to delete उनके संसार upon death.
minecraft received पाँच awards from the 2011 Game Developers सम्मेलन : it थी awarded the नवीनता Award, बेहतरीन downloadable खेल पुरस्कार, और the Best Debut Game पुरस्कार इससे the खेल Developers चुनाव पुरस्कार ; and the दर्शक Award, as well as the Seumas mcnally ग्रैंड Prize, from the स्वतंत्र खेल पर्व in 2011.
In 2012, minecraft was awarded a Golden Joystick Award in the श्रेणी बेहतरीन Downloadable खेल.
as of अप्रैल 8, 2013, the खेल has बेची over 10 लाख नक़ल on pc and as of January 22, 2013, over 20 million नक़ल across सब प्लेटफ़ॉर्म.
the Dark Knight is a 2008 british-american superhero फिल्मी निर्देशित, उत्पादित, and co-written by क्रिस्टोफर नोलन.
आधारित on the dc Comics character बैटमैन, the फिल्मी is the second भाग of नोलन 's Batman फिल्मी series and a sequel to 2005 's बैटमैन begins.
ईसाई Bale reprises the सीसे role of ब्रूस wayne/batman, with a returning डाल of माइकल Caine as अल्फ्रेड pennyworth, गेरी oldman as जेम्स Gordon and मॉर्गन फ्रीमैन as लुसियस फॉक्स.
The film introduces the अक्षर of Harvey डेंट ( Aaron eckhart ), गोथम 's newly निर्वाचित District Attorney और the consort of Bruce वेन 's childhood dost रेचल dawes ( मैगी Gyllenhaal ), जो joins बैटमैन और the police in combating the नई उठती threat of a दण्ड मास्टरमाइंड कॉलिंग himself `` The जोकर `` ( Heath Ledger ).
Nolan 's inspiration लिये the film थी the जोकर 's comic किताब डेब्यू in 1940, the 1988 graphic novel, and the 1996 श्रेणी, जिससे retold two-face 's origin.
the nickname `` the Dark Knight '' थी पहला applied to बैटमैन in Batman no. 1 ( 1940 ), in a स्टोरी written by विधेयक उंगली.
the Dark Knight थी फिल्माया primarily in शिकागो, as खूब as in अनेक अन्य locations in the United States, the United किंगडम, और हांग Kong.
नोलन used an IMAX कैमरा to फिल्मी कुछ sequences, सहित the जोकर 's पहला रूप in the फिल्मी.
on January 22, 2008, some महीने after he था समाप्त फिल्मांकन on the Dark Knight और छह months before the film 's रिलीज, झाड़ Ledger died इससे a विषाक्त संयोजन of नुस्खा drugs, अग्रणी to intense attention इससे the दबायें and movie-going पब्लिक.
warner Bros. था initially निर्मित a viral विपणन campaign लिये the अंधेरा Knight, developing promotional websites and trailers highlighting screen गोलियाँ of लेजर as the Joker, लकिन after लेजर 's death, the स्टुडियो refocused its promotional अभियान.
the अंधेरा Knight थी released on July 16, 2008 in Australia, on July 18, 2008 in उत्तर अमेरिका, and on July 24, 2008 in the संयुक्त किंगडम.
माना एक of the बेहतरीन films of the 2000s और एक of the बेहतरीन सुपरहीरो films कभी बना, the फिल्मी प्राप्त अत्यधिक धनात्मक reviews and नियत numerous records दौरान इसके theatrical चलाएं.
साथ over $ 1 अरब in आय worldwide, it is the 14th-highest-grossing film of सब time, unadjusted for महंगाई.

The Sydney ओपेरा हाउस is a multi-venue performing कला centre in नई दक्षिण वेल्स, Australia.
it थी conceived and largely built by डैनिश वास्तु jørn Utzon, opening in 1973 बाद a long gestation that began साथ उसके competition-winning design in 1957.
Joseph काहिल 's New दक्षिण वेल्स Government gave the go-ahead लिये work to शुरू in 1958.
The सरकारी 's bold निर्णय to चुनें utzon 's डिज़ाइन is प्रायः overshadowed by the scandal that followed.
it is on Bennelong पाइंट in सिडनी harbour, बंद to the Sydney harbour Bridge.
it sits at the northeastern टिप of the सिडनी सेंट्रल कारोबार ज़िला ( the सीबीडी ), घिरी on तीन पहलू by the harbour ( सिडनी कोव और फार्म Cove ) और inland by the royal botanic gardens.
Contrary to its नाम, it houses अनेक प्रदर्शन venues.
it is among the busiest performing arts centres in the world, hosting over 1,500 प्रदर्शन प्रत्येक year attended by some 1.2 million लोगों.
it provides a स्थान for अनेक performing-arts कंपनियाँ, including the चार कुंजी निवासी कंपनियाँ ओपेरा ऑस्ट्रेलिया, the Australian बैले, the Sydney थिएटर Company and the Sydney सिंफनी ऑर्केस्ट्रा, and presents a wide range of productions on इसके अपना account.
It is भी one of the most popular आगंतुक आकर्षण in ऑस्ट्रेलिया, साथ more than सात million people visiting प्रत्येक साल, 300,000 of whom take a guided tour.
it is administered by the सिडनी ओपेरा हाउस Trust, under the नई दक्षिण Wales Ministry of the Arts.
On 28 जून 2007, it was made a UNESCO World विरासत साईट.
it is one of the 20th century 's सबसे distinctive buildings और एक of the most famous performing arts केंद्रों in the संसार.
a graph of body mass अनुक्रमणिका as a फलन of देह द्रव्यमान and body height is shown above.
the dashed lines represent subdivisions within a प्रमुख class.
लिये उदाहरण the `` Underweight '' वर्गीकरण is further विभाजित into `` कठोर '', `` मॉडरेट '', and `` mild '' subclasses.
The देह mass अनुक्रमणिका ( बीएमआई ), or quetelet index, is a माप लिये इंसान देह आकार आधारित on an individual 's weight और ऊँचाई.
it was devised between 1830 and 1850 by the Belgian polymath Adolphe Quetelet दौरान the कोर्स of developing `` सोशल भौतिकी ''.
Body द्रव्यमान index is पारिभाषित as the individual 's देह mass विभाजित by the square of उनके ऊँचाई.
The formulae universally प्रयुक्त in medicine produce a ईकाई of माप of kg/m2.
BMI can भी be determined using a बीएमआई chart, जिससे प्रदर्शक BMI as a function of weight ( horizontal अक्ष ) and ऊँचाई ( लंबवत अक्ष ) using रुपरेखा lines लिये अलग मान of BMI or colors लिये अलग बीएमआई श्रेणी.
† the फ़ैक्टर लिये UK/US units is अधिक precisely 703.06957964, लकिन that स्तर of परिशुद्धता is नहीं meaningful लिये इस गणना.
To कार्य इससे stone और pounds पहला गुणा the स्टोन by 14 तब add the पाउंड to give the पूरे द्रव्यमान in pounds ; to work from feet और इंच पहला multiply the feet by 12 तब add the inches to दे the पूरे ऊँचाई in इंच.
थामस paine ( January 29, 1737 ( ns फ़रवरी 9, 1737 ) – जून 8, 1809 ) थी an english-american राजनैतिक activist, author, राजनैतिक theorist और क्रांतिकारी.
as the लेखक of दो highly influential pamphlets at the प्रारंभ of the अमरीकी क्रान्ति, he प्रेरित the देशप्रेमी in 1776 to declare स्वतंत्रता इससे ब्रिटेन.
उसके ideas reflected आत्मज्ञान era बयानबाजी of transnational इंसान अधिकारों.
he रै been पुकारा `` a corsetmaker by व्यापार, a journalist by व्यवसायिक, और a propagandist by inclination. ''
born in thetford, इंग्लैण्ड, in the काउंटी of नॉर्फ़ोक, paine emigrated to the अंग्रेजों American colonies in 1774 with the सहायता of बेंजामिन Franklin and he arrived in time to participate in the American क्रान्ति.
उसके principal योगदान were the powerful, widely पढ़ा pamphlet Common भाव ( 1776 ), the all-time best-selling अमरीकी किताब that advocated औपनिवेशिक अमेरिका 's independence from the किंगडम of Great Britain, और The अमरीकी संकट ( 1776–83 ), a pro-revolutionary pamphlet श्रेणी.
आम भाव थी so influential that जॉन Adams कहा, `` बगैर the कलम of the लेखक of आम भाव, the sword of वॉशिंगटन होता have been उठाया in vain.”
paine lived in फ़्रांस लिये most of the 1790s, बनने deeply involved in the फ्रेंच क्रान्ति.
He लिखा the अधिकारों of Man ( 1791 ), in भाग a defence of the फ्रेंच Revolution against its critics.
His attacks on अंग्रेजों writer Edmund Burke led to a विचारण and conviction in absentia in 1792 for the अपराधों of seditious मानहानि.
in 1792, despite नहीं होने समर्थ to बोलो फ्रेंच, he was निर्वाचित to the फ्रेंच नेशनल सम्मेलन.
the Girondists regarded उसे as an ally.
Consequently, the Montagnards, especially Robespierre, regarded him as an दुश्मन.
in दिसम्बर 1793, he थी arrested and imprisoned in Paris, then released in 1794.
he became notorious क्युकी of The आयु of कारण ( 1793–94 ), उसके किताब that अधिवक्ताओं देववाद, promotes कारण और freethinking, और argues विरूद्ध institutionalized धर्म in सामान्य और ईसाई doctrine in particular.
He भी लिखा the pamphlet कृषिक इंसाफ ( 1795 ), discussing the origins of प्रॉपर्टी, और introduced the अवधारणा of a गारंटी minimum आय.
In 1802, he लौटे to अमेरिका जहाँ he died on June 8, 1809.
Only छह people attended his अंत्येष्टि as he था been ostracized लिये his उपहास of Christianity.
Clinical trials are सेट of परीक्षण in medical research और ड्रग विकास that generate सुरक्षा और efficacy data ( or अधिक specifically, सूचना about प्रतिकूल drug reactions and प्रतिकूल effects of अन्य उपचार ) लिये स्वास्थ्य interventions ( e.g., drugs, diagnostics, डिवाइस, चिकित्सा प्रोटोकॉल ).
They हैं conducted तभी बाद संतोषजनक सूचना रै महरूम gathered on the विशेषता of the गैर नैदानिक सुरक्षा, और health authority/ethics कमेटी approval is granted in the country जहाँ स्वीकृति of the drug or यंत्र is sought.
previously, अनेक उभरते देशों did नहीं require लोकल ट्रायल for उत्पाद approvals.
अभी, हालांकि उभरते countries स्टिल accept आंकड़ा from u.s./europe, वे भी आवश्यकता कुछ लोकल trials.
depending on the type of product and the stage of its विकास, जांचकर्ताओं initially enroll volunteers and/or मरीजों into छोटी पायलट studies, और subsequently conduct larger scale studies in मरीजों that प्रायः compare the new product साथ others already स्वीकृत for the affliction of ब्याज.
as धनात्मक सुरक्षा और efficacy आंकड़ा हैं gathered, the number of patients is typically increased.
Clinical ट्रायल can vary in size, and can involve a single शोध एंटिटी in one देश or अनेक such entities in multiple देशों.
a full series of ट्रायल may incur sizable costs, and the burden of paying लिये सब the जरुरी लोगों और सेवाएं is प्रायः borne by the प्रायोजक, which may be a governmental संगठन or a pharmaceutical, biotechnology or चिकित्सा यंत्र कम्पनी.
When the विविधता of required support भूमिकाएँ exceeds the संसाधन of the प्रायोजक, a नैदानिक trial is managed by an outsourced संगी, ऐसे as a अनुबंध research organization or a clinical trials unit in the अकादमिक सेक्टर.
The Green खाड़ी Packers हैं an अमरीकी football team based in Green खाड़ी, विस्कॉन्सिन.
They हैं members of the उत्तर प्रभाग of the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल सम्मेलन ( nfc ) in the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल लीग ( एनएफएल ).
Green खाड़ी is the third-oldest मताधिकार in the एनएफएल, having महरूम व्यवस्थित और playing in 1919.
The पैकर्स हैं the only non-profit, community-owned major league पेशेवर खेल team in the संयुक्त States.
the पैकर्स are the पिछला vestige of `` छोटी कस्बा टीमों '' कि यहूद एकबार आम in the एनएफएल दौरान the 1920s और 1930s.
संस्थापित in 1919 by अर्ल `` घुंघराले '' Lambeau ( hence the name lambeau Field on जिससे the team plays ) और George व्हिटनी calhoun, the ग्रीन खाड़ी पैकर्स can ट्रेस their lineage to other semi-professional टीमों in Green खाड़ी dating back to 1896.
in 1919 और 1920 the पैकर्स competed as a semi-professional football टोली विरूद्ध क्लब इससे around विस्कॉन्सिन and the मिडवेस्ट.
They joined the अमरीकी Professional फ़ुटबॉल Association ( APFA ) in 1921, the forerunner to what is ज्ञात आज as the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल League ( एनएफएल ).
Although ग्रीन खाड़ी is the पिछला NFL `` small town '' टोली, its local fan base और media extends into आसपास Milwaukee ; the team also निभाई selected घर खेल वहीँ between 1933 और 1994.
the Green खाड़ी Packers have won 13 लीग championships ( अधिक than कोई अन्य टोली in the NFL ), including nine NFL championships prior to the सुपर Bowl era और four सुपर कटोरी victories —in 1967 ( सुपर Bowl i ), 1968 ( सुपर Bowl ii ), 1997 ( Super Bowl xxxi ) and 2011 ( Super Bowl XLV ).
the पैकर्स have long-standing, कड़वा rivalries with उनके NFC North ( formerly the NFC सेंट्रल ) प्रतिद्वंद्वियों, the शिकागो bears, Minnesota Vikings and the डेट्रॉयट Lions.
the bears-packers फंसने is एक of the oldest rivalries in NFL history, dating वापस to 1921.
इथेनॉल fuel is इथेनॉल ( ethyl दारू ), the same type of alcohol मिला in alcoholic पेय.
It is most प्रायः used as a motor fuel, मुख्यतः as a biofuel additive for गैसोलीन.
World ethanol production लिये transport ईंधन tripled between 2000 and 2007 इससे 17 अरब to अधिक than 52 अरब liters.
इससे 2007 to 2008, the share of ethanol in वैश्विक गैसोलीन type fuel use increased from 3.7 % to 5.4 %.
in 2011 worldwide इथेनॉल ईंधन उत्पादन पहुँचे 22.36 अरब u.S. द्रव gallons ( bg ) ( 84.6 अरब liters ), साथ the संयुक्त States as the शीर्ष निर्माता with 13.9 bg ( 52.6 अरब liters ), accounting लिये 62.2 % of global उत्पादन, followed by ब्राज़ील with 5.6 bg ( 21.1 अरब liters ).
Ethanol ईंधन has a `` गैसोलीन gallon equivalency `` ( GGE ) value of, जिससे अर्थात् 1.5 गैलन of ethanol produce the उर्जा of एक गैलन of गैसोलीन.
Ethanol fuel is widely प्रयुक्त in ब्राज़ील और in the संयुक्त States, and साथ both देशों were जिम्मेदार लिये 87.1 % of the संसार 's ethanol ईंधन उत्पादन in 2011.
सबसे cars on the road today in the U.S. can run on मिश्रणों of up to 10 % इथेनॉल, और इथेनॉल represented 10 % of the u.S. गैसोलीन fuel supply derived from domestic स्त्रोत in 2011.
चूंकि 1976 the Brazilian सरकारी has बना it अनिवार्य to मिश्रण ethanol with गैसोलीन, and चूंकि 2007 the legal मिश्रण is around 25 % इथेनॉल और 75 % गैसोलीन ( E25 ).
By December 2011 ब्राज़ील था a fleet of 14.8 million flex-fuel automobiles and light ट्रक and 1.5 लाख flex-fuel मोटरसाइकिल that regularly use neat ethanol ईंधन ( known as e100 ).
bioethanol is a रूप of renewable उर्जा that can be produced from agricultural feedstocks.
It can be बना इससे very common फसलों ऐसे as sugar cane, potato, manioc and corn.
There रै महरूम considerable बहस about how उपयोगी bioethanol will be in replacing गैसोलीन.
चिंताएं about its उत्पादन and use relate to increased food prices due to the large राशि of arable जमीन required लिये फसलों, as खूब as the उर्जा and pollution संतुलन of the पूरे साईकिल of ethanol उत्पादन, विशेषकर from corn.
Recent developments साथ cellulosic इथेनॉल उत्पादन and commercialization may allay some of these चिंताएं.
cellulosic इथेनॉल offers promise because cellulose मछली, a major and universal घटक in plant cells दीवारें, can be प्रयुक्त to उपज इथेनॉल.
according to the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Energy एजेंसी, cellulosic इथेनॉल could allow इथेनॉल fuels to play a much bigger भूमिका in the भविष्य than previously thought.

a प्लैक commemorating the स्थान of the Sarajevo हत्या and steps of Gavrilo Princip ( image लिया in 1987, पहले कदम यहूद removed in 1992 और प्लैक बदला from Cyrillic to लैटिन स्क्रिप्ट )
