On 28 जून 1914, archduke फ्रांज फर्डिनेंड of ऑस्ट्रिया, वारिस presumptive to the austro-hungarian सिंहासन, और उसके wife, Sophie, Duchess of hohenberg, यहूद शॉट मुर्दे in साराजेवो, by Gavrilo princip, एक of a समूह of six बोस्नियाई serb हत्यारे coordinated by डेनियल Ilić.
The राजनैतिक objective of the हत्या थी to break बंद Austria-Hungary 's south-slav प्रांतों so वे could be संयुक्त into a वृहद Serbia or a यूगोस्लाविया.
the assassins ' motives यहूद सतत साथ the गति कि later became known as यंग Bosnia.
Serbian सैन्य अधिकारियों stood पीछे the attack.
At the शीर्ष of these सर्बियाई सैन्य षड्यंत्रकारियों थी Chief of सर्बियाई Military प्रज्ञा Dragutin dimitrijević, his righthand man Major Vojislav Tankosić, and masterspy rade Malobabić.
प्रमुख tankosić armed the हत्यारे साथ बम and pistols and प्रशिक्षित them.
The हत्यारे यहूद given अभिगम to the same clandestine टनल of safe-houses and एजेंटों कि Rade malobabić प्रयुक्त लिये the घुसपैठ of हथियार और operatives into austria-hungary.
The हत्यारे, the key सदस्यों of the clandestine टनल, और the key सर्बियाई सैन्य षड्यंत्रकारियों जो यहूद still जिंदा were गिरफ्तार, आजमाया, convicted और punished.
those जो यहूद arrested in बोस्निया were tried in Sarajevo in अक्तूबर 1914.
The अन्य conspirators were गिरफ्तार and tried before a Serbian कंगारू court on the French-controlled salonika Front in 1916–1917 on unrelated false आरोप ; सर्बिया चलाया तीन of the शीर्ष सैन्य षड्यंत्रकारियों.
much of कया is ज्ञात परिचय the assassinations आता from ये दो ट्रायल and related रिकॉर्ड.
कार्यभार of जिम्मेदारी लिये the bombing and हत्याएं of 28 June is अत्यधिक controversial क्युकी the आक्रमण led to the outbreak of संसार War i एक month later.
Renée कैथलीन zellweger ( born अप्रैल 25, 1969 ) is an American अभिनेत्री और producer.
zellweger first gained widespread attention लिये her भूमिका in the फिल्मी जेरी मैग्वायर ( 1996 ), and subsequently received two nominations लिये the Academy पुरस्कार लिये Best अभिनेत्री लिये her roles as Bridget जोन्स in the comedy ब्रिजेट जोन्स 's डायरी ( 2001 ), and as roxie हार्ट in the musical शिकागो ( 2002 ).
वो जीती the अकादमी पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन Supporting अभिनेत्री लिये उसके performance in the drama ठंडा Mountain ( 2003 ).
She रै जीती an अकादमी पुरस्कार, three सुनहरी Globe Awards, तीन Screen अभिनेताओं गिल्ड पुरस्कार, और a bafta Award ; थी named hasty खीर 's स्त्री of the साल in 2009 ; और established herself as एक of the highest-paid हॉलीवुड अभिनेत्रियों as of 2007.
The ossicles ( भी पुकारा auditory ossicles ) are the three smallest हड्डियों in the human body, the malleus, the incus and the stapes.
They are contained भीतर the मध्य कान स्पेस and serve to transmit ध्वनि इससे the एयर to the fluid-filled labyrinth ( cochlea ).
The अनुपस्थिति of the auditory ossicles होता constitute a moderate-to-severe hearing loss.
the पद `` ossicles '' वस्तुतः अर्थात् `` tiny bones '' and commonly refers to the auditory ossicles, हालांकि the term may refer to कोई small bone throughout the body.
the New Covenant ( Hebrew • • — यूनानी • • diatheke kaine ) is a biblical निर्वचन originally निकला इससे a phrase in the Book of यिर्मयाह, in the Hebrew शास्त्रों.
it is often thought of as an eschatological मुक्तिदाता Age or world to come and is सम्बन्धित to the biblical concept of the किंगडम of God.
generally, ईसाइयों believe कि the नई Covenant थी instituted at the Last Supper as भाग of the eucharist, जिससे in the इन्जील of John includes the नई commandment.
वहीँ हैं अनेक ईसाई eschatologies that further define the नई Covenant, as an उदाहरण an उदघाटन eschatology defines और describes the New वचन as an जारी relationship between ईसाई ईमानवालों और God कि will be in full फलीभूत बाद the दूसरी coming of Christ ; that is, it होगा नहीं तभी be in full फलीभूत in believing दिल, लकिन in the भविष्य बाह्य संसार as well.
the connection between the रक्त of मसीह और the New वचन is seen in सबसे आधुनिक अंग्रेज़ी translations of the New वसीयत साथ the saying : `` this कप कि is poured आउट लिये you is the new वचन in my रक्त ''.
Christians believe कि यीशु is the मध्यस्थ of the New वचन, और that the रक्त of मसीह शेड at उसके crucifixion is the जरूरी रक्त of the covenant.
as with सब covenants between परमेश्वर और man described in the बाइबल, the नई वचन is माना `` a बंध in रक्त sovereignly administered by परमेश्वर. ''
it रै been theorized कि the New वचन is the Law of मसीह as बोला दौरान his Sermon on the Mount.
the following सूची of लोगों pardoned or granted दया by the अध्यक्ष of the United States documents the सबसे prominent मामले of प्रत्येक presidency.
as granted by the संविधान ( Article II, Section 2, Clause 1 ), राष्ट्रपतियों have the power to ग्रान्ट दया in एक or अधिक of the following तरीके : the क्षमता to ग्रान्ट a full pardon, to commute a वाक्य, or to rescind a ठीक.
u.S. Presidents have no power to grant दया लिये अपराधों prosecuted under राज्य विधि.
as to the difference between a pardon and a commutation:
a pardon is an कार्यपालिका अनुक्रम vacating a conviction.
a commutation is the शमन of the वाक्य of किसी फिलहाल serving a sentence लिये a अपराधों pursuant to a conviction, without vacating the conviction itself.
लगभग 20,000 pardons और clemencies were जारी by u.S. presidents in the 20th century alone.
the records of अधिनियमों of दया were public जबतक 1934.
in 1981 the दफ्तर of the Pardon attorney was निर्मित और records इससे अध्यक्ष H. W. बुश आगे हैं now सूचीबद्ध.
This सूची includes pardons और commutations.
tampa ( ) is a नगर in the U.S. state of Florida.
it serves as the county सीट लिये Hillsborough काउंटी और is स्तिथ on the वेस्ट coast of Florida, on tampa Bay near the Gulf of Mexico.
the जनसांख्यिकी of Tampa in 2011 थी 346,037.
The वर्तमान location of tampa थी एकबार inhabited by स्वदेशी peoples of the सुरक्षा हार्बर culture, सबसे notably the tocobaga and the pohoy, जो जिया साथ the shores of Tampa Bay.
it थी briefly explored by स्पेनी explorers in the जल्दी 16th century, लकिन there यहूद no permanent अमरीकी or यूरोपीय settlements भीतर आज 's नगर हद until after the संयुक्त राज्य था acquired फ्लोरिडा इससे स्पेन in 1819.
in 1824, the United राज्य Army स्थापित a frontier चौकी called Fort Brooke at the मुँह of the hillsborough नदी, निकट the साईट of today 's tampa सम्मेलन बीच.
The first civilian निवासियों were pioneers who settled near the फोर्ट for सुरक्षा इससे the आसपास seminole जनसांख्यिकी.
the town grew धीरे until the 1880s, जब रेलरोड कड़ी, the डिस्कवरी of फास्फेट, और the arrival of the cigar उद्योग jump-started Tampa 's विकास और helped it to grow into an महत्वपूर्ण नगर by the जल्दी 1900s.
आज, tampa is a part of the महानगर क्षेत्रफल सबसे commonly referred to as the tampa खाड़ी क्षेत्रफल.
लिये u.S. Census उद्देश्य, Tampa is भाग of the Tampa-St. petersburg-clearwater, फ्लोरिडा महानगर सांख्यिकीय Area.
The four-county area is composed of roughly 2.7 million निवासियों, making it the दूसरी largest metropolitan सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रफल ( MSA ) in the राज्य, और the चौथी largest in the southeastern संयुक्त राज्य, पीछे मियामी, वॉशिंगटन, d.C., और Atlanta.
the वृहद tampa Bay क्षेत्रफल रै just over 4 लाख residents और generally includes the Tampa और Sarasota मैट्रो areas.
the tampa खाड़ी Partnership और U.S. Census आंकड़ा showed an average सालाना विकास of 2.47 प्रतिशत, or a gain of लगभग 97,000 निवासियों प्रति year.
between 2000 और 2006, the वृहद tampa खाड़ी Market अनुभवी a combined growth रेट of 14.8 percent, growing from 3.4 लाख to 3.9 million और hitting the 4 लाख लोगों mark on अप्रैल 1, 2007.
a 2012 अनुमान shows the tampa खाड़ी क्षेत्रफल population to have 4,310,524 लोगों and a 2017 प्रक्षेप of 4,536,854 लोगों.
tampa रै a क्रमांक of खेल teams, ऐसे as the tampa Bay buccaneers of the नेशनल Football League, the Tampa खाड़ी Lightning of the नेशनल Hockey लीग, और the Tampa खाड़ी तूफ़ान of the एरिना Football League.
The tampa Bay किरणें in Major लीग Baseball और the tampa खाड़ी Rowdies of the उत्तर अमरीकी सॉकर League play उनके घर खेल in neighboring st. Petersburg, फ्लोरिडा.
In 2008, tampa was क्रमित as the 5th बेहतरीन outdoor city by Forbes.
a 2004 सर्वेक्षण by the nyu newspaper वॉशिंगटन वर्गाकार News क्रमित Tampa as a शीर्ष city लिये `` twenty-somethings. ''
tampa is now ranked as a `` Gamma '' संसार नगर by Loughborough विश्वविद्यालयों.
according to Loughborough, tampa ranks alongside other संसार शहरों ऐसे as फीनिक्स, सेंटो Domingo, and ओसाका.
in हाल years Tampa has देखी a notable upsurge in high-market माँग इससे उपभोक्ता, signaling अधिक माल concentrated in the क्षेत्रफल.
Tampa hosted the 2012 Republican National सम्मेलन.
the शेवरलेट Cavalier was a कॉम्पैक्ट ऑटोमोबाइल produced इससे 1982 to 2005 by General मोटर्स.
Built on the company 's J मंच, the Cavalier उत्पादित the उच्चतम बिक्री in 1984.
AT & t Mobility LLC branded and referred to as AT & T ( formerly cingular बेतार LLC ), is a wholly owned subsidiary of at & t inc. कि provides बेतार services to 107 million subscribers in the संयुक्त राज्य, सहित प्यूर्टो Rico and the u.S. Virgin आइलैंड्स.
AT & t गतिशीलता is the दूसरी largest बेतार telecommunications प्रदाता in the संयुक्त States और Puerto Rico, पीछे verizon Wireless, which serves 115.78 लाख ग्राहक as of the चौथी क्वार्टर of 2012.
AT & T गतिशीलता is headquartered in the lenox पार्क क्षेत्रफल of dekalb Co. Georgia, just outside अटलांटा.
originally Cingular Wireless llc इससे 2000 to 2007, a joint venture between sbc संचार and bellsouth, the कम्पनी acquired the old at & T Wireless in 2004 ; sbc later acquired the original at & t और re-branded as `` at & T ''.
cingular became wholly स्वामित्व by AT & t in December 2006 as a result of at & t 's acquisition of bellsouth.
In January 2007, Cingular पुष्टि it होता re-brand itself under the AT & T नाम.
हालांकि the विधिक corporate नाम change occurred immediately, लिये दोनो नियामक और brand-awareness reasons both ब्रांड्स were प्रयुक्त in the कम्पनी 's signage और advertising दौरान a transition काल.
The परिवर्तन concluded in late जून, just prior to the rollout of the Apple iphone.
On March 20, 2011, at & t Mobility announced इसके intention to acquire T-Mobile यूएसए from डॉयचे Telekom लिये $ 39 billion.
If it had प्राप्त सरकारी and regulatory approval, AT & T होता have had अधिक than 130 लाख subscribers.
however, the u.S. Department of इंसाफ, the संघीय Communications आयोग, और AT & t गतिशीलता 's competitors ( ऐसे as Sprint nextel ) opposed the move on the grounds that it होता reduce competition in the सेल्यूलर संचार market.
in दिसम्बर 2011, in the फेस of both सरकारी और फैली उपभोक्ता विपक्ष, AT & t withdrew उनके प्रस्ताव to पूरा the विलय.
Martin लूथर किंग, Jr. ( January 15, 1929 – अप्रैल 4, 1968 ) थी an अमरीकी clergyman, activist, and नेता in the African-American सिविल अधिकारों Movement.
He is बेहतरीन ज्ञात for his भूमिका in the advancement of civil अधिकारों using nonviolent सिविल disobedience.
King रै become a नेशनल icon in the history of American प्रगतिवाद.
a Baptist मंत्री, किंग became a civil rights activist जल्दी in उसके career.
he led the 1955 मोंटगोमरी बस बहिष्कार और helped मिला the दक्षिणी Christian Leadership सम्मेलन ( sclc ) in 1957, serving as इसके first अध्यक्ष.
With the sclc, किंग led an unsuccessful संघर्ष against पृथक्करण in albany, जॉर्जिया, in 1962, और organized nonviolent विरोध in बर्मिंघम, Alabama, कि आकर्षित नेशनल ध्यान following television न्यूज कवरेज of the क्रूर police जवाब.
King भी helped to व्यवस्थित the 1963 कूच on Washington, जहाँ he वितरित उसके `` I have a सपना `` speech.
वहीँ, he स्थापित his प्रतिष्ठा as एक of the महानतम orators in अमरीकी history.
he भी स्थापित his प्रतिष्ठा as a कट्टरपंथी, और became an ऑब्जेक्ट of the संघीय Bureau of छानबीन 's cointelpro for the बाकी of उसके जीवन.
एफबीआई एजेंटों investigated him for possible कम्युनिस्ट ties, अंकित his extramarital liaisons and reported on them to सरकारी officials, और on one अवसर, mailed किंग a threatening anonymous letter that he interpreted as an attempt to make उसे commit suicide.
On October 14, 1964, किंग प्राप्त the Nobel सलाम पुरस्कार लिये combating जातिगत असमानता through nonviolence.
in 1965, he and the sclc helped to organize the Selma to मोंटगोमरी marches और the following साल, he took the movement उत्तर to शिकागो.
In the final सालो of his life, किंग विस्तारित his फ़ोकस to शामिल गरीबी और the Vietnam युद्ध, alienating many of his उदार allies with a 1967 speech titled `` परे Vietnam ''.
King was नियोजन a नेशनल occupation of वॉशिंगटन, d.C., पुकारा the ग़रीब People 's अभियान.
किंग थी assassinated on अप्रैल 4, 1968, in Memphis, टेनेसी.
उसके death was followed by riots in अनेक U.S. शहरों.
Allegations कि James अर्ल Ray, the man convicted of हत्या किंग, था महरूम framed or acted in concert with government एजेंटों persisted for decades बाद the shooting, और the jury of a 1999 सिविल विचारण मिला Loyd Jowers to be complicit in a षड्यंत्र विरूद्ध किंग.
King was awarded the Presidential पदक of Freedom और the congressional सुनहरा पदक मरणोपरांत.
Martin लूथर King, jr. Day was established as a U.S. संघीय अवकाश in 1986.
Hundreds of streets in the u.S. have been renamed in उसके honor.

The बाघ ( पेंथेरा tigris ) is the largest cat प्रजाति, reaching a कुल body लंबाई of up to और weighing up to.
it is the third largest land carnivore ( पीछे तभी the polar भालू और the brown bear ).
इसके सबसे recognizable विशेषता is a पैटर्न of dark लंबवत धारियाँ on reddish-orange फर साथ a lighter underside.
it रै exceptional stout दांत, and the canines are the longest among living felids साथ a क्राउन ऊँचाई of as much as or भी.
In zoos, टाइगर्स have lived for 20 to 26 सालो, which also seems to be their आयु in the जंगली.
वे हैं territorial and generally एकान्त लकिन सोशल animals, often requiring large संलग्न areas of habitat कि support उनके prey requirements.
इस, coupled with the फैक्ट कि they हैं स्वदेशी to some of the more densely आबादी places on धरती, has caused significant विरोध with इंसानो.
टाइगर्स once ranged widely आरपार Asia, इससे तुर्कों in the वेस्ट to the eastern coast of रूस.
Over the past 100 सालो, they have lost 93 % of their ऐतिहासिक दायरा, और have महरूम extirpated इससे दक्षिणपश्चिम and central एशिया, from the आइलैंड्स of जावा and bali, and इससे विशाल क्षेत्रों of southeast और Eastern Asia.
आज, वे दायरा इससे the Siberian ताइगा to खोलें grasslands और tropical mangrove swamps.
the बाकी छह बाघ subspecies have been classified as endangered by आईयूसीएन.
The वैश्विक जनसांख्यिकी in the wild is estimated to क्रमांक between 3,062 और 3,948 individuals, bas इससे around 100,000 at the प्रारंभ of the 20th सदी, साथ सबसे remaining populations occurring in छोटी pockets isolated from प्रत्येक अन्य.
प्रमुख कारण for जनसांख्यिकी मनाही शामिल आवास destruction, आवास fragmentation और poaching.
the extent of क्षेत्रफल occupied by टाइगर्स is estimated at कम than, a 41 % decline from the क्षेत्रफल estimated in the mid-1990s.
टाइगर्स are among the सबसे recognisable और लोकप्रिय of the संसार 's charismatic महाप्राणी.
वे have प्रदर्शित prominently in प्राचीन mythology और लोकगीत, and continue to be चित्रित in आधुनिक films and literature.
टाइगर्स appear on अनेक flags, coats of arms, and as mascots for sporting teams.
The बंगाल बाघ is the national एनिमल of दोनो इण्डिया and बांग्लादेश.
the सरलीकृत आतंरिक structure of a chloroplast
अवलोकन of the calvin cycle and कार्बन fixation
the light-independent reactions of photosynthesis हैं रासायनिक reactions that बदलें carbon डाइऑक्साइड और other compounds into ग्लूकोज.
ये प्रतिक्रियाएँ occur in the stroma, the fluid-filled area of a हरितलवक बाहर of the thylakoid membranes.
ये reactions लो the light-dependent प्रतिक्रियाएँ और perform further रासायनिक प्रक्रियाओं on them.
वहीँ हैं three phases to the light-independent reactions, collectively पुकारा the Calvin साईकिल : कार्बन fixation, कटौती प्रतिक्रियाएँ, and ribulose 1,5-bisphosphate ( RuBP ) regeneration.
despite its name, this process occurs तभी जब लाइट is उपलब्धियाँ.
पौधे do not carry आउट the Calvin साईकिल by रात्रि.
वे, बजाय, रिलीज sucrose into the phloem from their मंड reserves.
This process happens when light is उपलब्धियाँ independent of the दयालु of photosynthesis ( c3 कार्बन fixation, C4 कार्बन fixation, और crassulacean Acid Metabolism ) ; कैम plants स्टोर malic acid in उनके vacuoles every रात्रि और रिलीज it by day in अनुक्रम to मेक this process work.
a लिनेन रूमाल साथ pulled लड़ी embroidery around the किनारे
Linen cloth बरामद इससे Qumran Cave 1 near the Dead Sea.
Linen ( ) is a वस्त्र बना इससे the fibers of the flax plant, linum usitatissimum.
लिनेन is labor-intensive to manufacture, लकिन जब it is made into garments, it is valued लिये इसके exceptional coolness और ताजगी in hot weather.
The word `` linen '' is of West germanic origin and cognates साथ the लैटिन name लिये the flax संयंत्र linum, और the पहले यूनानी λινόν ( linon ).
This शब्द इतिहास रै दिए वृद्धि to a क्रमांक of अन्य terms in अंग्रेज़ी, the सबसे notable of जिससे is the अंग्रेज़ी शब्द लकीर, निकला from the use of a लिनेन ( flax ) thread to determine a सीधा line.
Textiles in a लिनेन बुनते बनावट, भी when बना of कपास, hemp और other non-flax मछली हैं also loosely referred to as `` लिनेन ''.
Such fabrics generally have उनके अपना specific names अन्य than लिनेन ; लिये example, fine कपास yarn in a linen-style बुनते is पुकारा madapolam.
the सामूहिक term `` linens `` is still often प्रयुक्त generically to describe a क्लास of woven और भी knitted bed, bath, तालिका और रसोईघर वस्त्र.
The name linens is retained क्युकी traditionally, linen थी used लिये many of ये items.
in the पास्ट, the शब्द `` linens '' थी भी प्रयुक्त to औसत lightweight undergarments such as shirts, chemises, waistshirts, lingerie ( a शब्द भी cognate साथ लिनेन ), और detachable कमीज़ छल्लों and cuffs, जिससे were historically बना लगभग exclusively आउट of लिनेन.
the अंदर cloth परत of fine composite clothing garments ( as for उदाहरण jackets ) was traditionally बना of लिनेन, and इस is the उत्पत्ति of the word अस्तर.
लिनेन वस्त्र appear to be कुछ of the oldest in the world : their इतिहास goes वापस many thousands of years.
Fragments of स्ट्रॉ, seeds, fibers, yarns, और विभिन्न प्रकार of fabrics जिससे date वापस to about 8000 bc have been मिला in Swiss lake dwellings.
dyed flax fibers found in a प्रागैतिहासिक cave in जॉर्जिया suggest the उपयोग of woven लिनेन fabrics from जंगली flax may तिथि वापस भी earlier to 36,000 bp.
लिनेन थी sometimes used as करेंसी in ancient Egypt.
मिश्र mummies were लपेटा in लिनेन क्युकी it थी देखी as a प्रतीक of लाइट और पवित्रता, और as a display of माल.
कुछ of ये fabrics, woven इससे हाथ spun yarns, were बहुत fine लिये उनके दिन, but हैं coarse compared to modern linen.
Today, linen is प्रायः an expensive textile, और is produced in अपेक्षाकृत छोटी quantities.
It has a long `` स्टेपल '' ( व्यक्तिगत रेशा length ) सापेक्ष to कपास और अन्य natural मछली.
अनेक उत्पाद हैं बना of linen : aprons, बैग, तौलिये ( swimmers, bath, beach, देह और धो तौलिये ), napkins, bed linens, लिनेन tablecloths, धावक, chair कवर, और men 's & महिलाओं 's wear.
The फीफा संसार कप, often बस the संसार कप, is an अंतरराष्ट्रीय association फ़ुटबॉल competition contested by the senior मेन 's national टीमों of the सदस्यों of fédération Internationale de फ़ुटबॉल Association ( फीफा ), the खेल 's वैश्विक शासी body.
the championship रै been awarded प्रत्येक चार सालो since the inaugural टूर्नामेंट in 1930, मगर in 1942 and 1946 जब it was नहीं held क्युकी of the Second World युद्ध.
the वर्तमान champions हैं Spain, जो जीती the 2010 टूर्नामेंट.
the वर्तमान स्वरूप of the tournament involves 32 टीमों स्पर्धा लिये the शीर्षक at venues भीतर the मेजबान nation ( s ) over a काल of about a माह ; इस phase is प्रायः पुकारा the संसार Cup फाइनल.
A योग्यता phase, which फिलहाल takes place over the preceding तीन सालो, is used to determine जिससे टीमों qualify लिये the टूर्नामेंट साथ with the मेजबान स्वदेश ( s ).
The 19 World Cup tournaments have महरूम जीती by आठ अलग national teams.

Consolidated city-counties represent a पृथक प्रकार of सरकारी कि includes the संपूर्ण population of a county, or county equivalent.
कुछ consolidated city-counties, however, शामिल अनेक incorporated स्थान.

Nintendo ds भंडार devices हैं devices प्रयुक्त to स्टोर a licensed डेवलपर 's work-in-progress बिंब, homebrew वीडियो games और डाउनलोड commercial games ( since the Nintendo DS is नहीं बेची साथ a rewritable भंडार मीडियम ).
licensed डेवलपर, however, can use a ब्लू बुद्धिमान प्रणालियों नाइट्रो Emulator बक्सा to फ्लैश cards.
ये डिवाइस हैं भी known as `` flashcarts '' or `` flashcards ''.
वहीँ हैं दो main वर्ग of flashcarts : older डिवाइस जिससे अनुरूप in slot-2 ( the खेल Boy Advance Game पाक slot ) and नए डिवाइस कि fit in Slot-1 ( the DS Game कार्ड slot ).
slot-2 ( or first-generation ) devices have महरूम historically सस्ता due to economies of स्केल ( inherited इससे उनके उपयोग साथ खेल लड़के Advance ), लकिन आवश्यकता a booting tool in Slot-1 in order to उपयोग the टच स्क्रीन and other ds सुविधाएँ.
second-generation डिवाइस ( those जिससे only use Slot-1 ) do नहीं कार्य with gba homebrew, but became कम expensive और easier to उपयोग, rivaling many slot-2 डिवाइस in दाम.
First-generation डिवाइस शामिल gba flash cartridges, gbamp cf, SuperCard, और m3.
second-generation devices शामिल r4 क्रान्ति, cyclods, g6 रियल और DS-X.
the storage यंत्र either contains फ्लैश memory or a स्लॉट लिये a मेमोरी card to स्टोर homebrew.
भंडार डिवाइस with a memory-card स्लॉट usually have more भंडार क्षमता than flash-memory डिवाइस.
हालांकि flash-memory capacity is प्रायः measured in megabits ( mb ), memory-card क्षमता is प्रायः measured in मेगाबाइट ( mb ) ( where 8 mb is 1 mb ).
Storage-device brands differ in their support लिये homebrew ; ds and खेल Boy अग्रिम ROMs ; special सुविधाएँ ( ऐसे as ability to खेल मीडिया फाइलें ) ; शारीरिक आकार और लागत.
सख्ती speaking, a storage device is not जरुरी लिये ds साथ FlashMe installed क्युकी homebrew can be भेजा to the DS using WMB.
However, इस is not an easily-portable विधि क्युकी the ds needs to be within दायरा of a suitable wi-fi कार्ड.

Geocaching is an outdoor recreational कार्यकलाप, in जिससे the भागीदार use a Global positioning System ( gps ) receiver or mobile यंत्र और अन्य navigational techniques to छुपा and seek containers, called `` geocaches '' or `` caches '', anywhere in the संसार.
A ठेठ cache is a small waterproof संग्राहक containing a logbook where the geocacher enters the date they मिला it और लक्षण it साथ उनके स्थापित कोड नाम.

a municipal बंध is a bond issued by a local सरकारी, or उनके agencies.
Potential issuers of नगरपालिका bonds include states, शहरों, counties, redevelopment एजेंसियों, special-purpose districts, स्कूल जिले, पब्लिक utility जिले, सरेआम स्वामित्व एयरपोर्ट and seaports, and कोई अन्य सरकारी एंटिटी ( or समूह of governments ) at or below the state स्तर.
नगरपालिका bonds may be general दायित्वों of the जारीकर्ता or secured by specified revenues.
in the United States, ब्याज income received by धारकों of नगरपालिका bonds is प्रायः exempt from the संघीय आय कर और इससे the आय कर of the राज्य in which वे are जारी, हालांकि नगरपालिका bonds issued लिये certain purposes may not be tax exempt.
Unlike नई issue stocks कि हैं brought to मार्केट साथ दाम प्रतिबंध जबतक the deal is sold, नगरपालिका bonds are फ़्री to trade at कोई समय एकबार वे हैं खरीदा by the investor.
पेशेवर traders regularly trade and retrade the वही bonds अनेक टाइम्स a सप्ताह.

The अंतरजाल फिल्म Database ( आईएमडीबी ) is an ऑनलाइन डेटाबेस of सूचना सम्बन्धित to films, television कार्यक्रम, और वीडियो खेल.

It is एक of the सबसे लोकप्रिय ऑनलाइन entertainment destinations, साथ over 100 million unique उपयोक्ता each month and a solid and rapidly growing मोबाईल उपस्थिति.

fibre चैनल मेजबान बस Adapter ( 64-bit pci-x कार्ड )
scsi Host बस एडाप्टर ( 16-bit ISA कार्ड )
in कंप्यूटर हार्डवेयर, a host controller, मेजबान एडाप्टर, or मेजबान bus एडाप्टर ( hba ) connects a मेजबान system ( the कंप्यूटर ) to other संजाल और भंडार डिवाइस.
The शर्तें are primarily प्रयुक्त to refer to devices लिये connecting scsi, fibre चैनल and esata devices.
However, डिवाइस लिये connecting to आईडीई, ईथरनेट, firewire, usb और other प्रणालियों may also be called मेजबान adapters.
recently, the आगमन of iSCSI और fibre Channel over ईथरनेट रै brought परिचय ईथरनेट HBAs, जिससे हैं अलग इससे ईथरनेट nics in कि they include TCP offload Engines.
वहीँ हैं also converged hbas that support both Ethernet and Fibre चैनल called Converged संजाल adapters ( CNAs ).
Cashmere स्कार्फ
आधुनिक मेन 's cashmere sweaters लिये बिक्री.
Cashmere ऊन, प्रायः simply ज्ञात as cashmere, is a रेशा obtained from cashmere goats और other types of बकरी.
the शब्द cashmere गर्भाशयी इससे an बूढ़ा स्पेलिंग of काश्मीर.
cashmere is ठीक in texture, strong, लाइट, and नरम.
Garments बना इससे it provide बेहतरीन इन्सुलेशन.
In the संयुक्त राज्य, under the U.S. Wool उत्पाद labeling Act of 1939, as amended, ( 15 uction 68b ( a ) ( 6 ) ), राज्य that a wool or textile product may not be labeled as containing cashmere unless:
ऐसे wool उत्पाद is the ठीक ( dehaired ) undercoat मछली उत्पादित by a cashmere goat ( capra hircus laniger ) ;
the औसत diameter of the रेशा of ऐसे ऊन उत्पाद does नहीं exceed 19 माइक्रोन ; और
such ऊन उत्पाद करता नहीं contain अधिक than 3 percent ( by weight ) of cashmere मछली with औसत diameters कि exceed 30 microns.
the औसत रेशा व्यास may be विषय to a गुणांक of विभिन्नता around the औसत कि shall नहीं exceed 24 percent.

Pain and कष्ट is the विधिक पद for the शारीरिक and emotional stress caused इससे an injury ( देखिए also पीड़ा और कष्ट ).

In a suit, पीड़ा और suffering is part of the `` सामान्य क्षतिपूर्ति '' section of the claimant 's अर्जी, or, alternatively, it is an element of `` compensatory '' non-economic damages that allows recovery for the दिमागी anguish and/or physical pain endured by the claimant as a result of चोट for which the plaintiff seeks परितोष.
अलावा इससे money damages awarded in विचारण, धन क्षतिपूर्ति are also दिए informally outside the न्यायिक system in mediations, arbitration ( both of जिससे may be अदालत annexed or non litigated दावा ) as खूब as in दिनचर्या insurance settlements.

Sample of a medallion signature गारंटी stampIn
the संयुक्त राज्य और Canada, a medallion signature guarantee is a special signature गारंटी लिये the transfer of securities.
it is a guarantee by the transferring financial institution कि the हस्ताक्षर is वास्तविक and the financial संस्था स्वीकृत देयता for कोई forgery.
हस्ताक्षर guarantees protect शेयरधारकों by preventing unauthorized transfers और possible निवेशकों नुकसान.
They also सीमा the देयता of the transfer एजेंट जो स्वीकृत the प्रमाणपत्र.
Different संस्थानों have अलग नीतियों as to what प्रकार of identification they आवश्यकता to provide the guarantee and whether वे चार्ज a fee लिये ऐसे सेवा ( प्रायः nominal if any ).
सबसे institutions will नहीं guarantee a हस्ताक्षर of किसी who रै नहीं already महरूम their ग्राहक.
A medallion हस्ताक्षर गारंटी is नहीं the same as an acknowledgment by a notary public, in the भाव that a `` हस्ताक्षर गारंटी '' is a प्रमाणन by the संस्था कि the हस्ताक्षर is प्रामाणिक, और an acknowledgment is a प्रमाणन by a नोटरी public attesting कि the signer signed a दस्तावेज़ voluntarily.
कुछ banks may no longer provide this सेवा, however, अनेक स्टिल do as खूब as अन्य वित्तीय institutions ऐसे as a बचत and लोन and क्रेडिट Unions.
At उनके एकमात्र discretion, these संस्थानों may स्टिल मनाही to provide the Medallion हस्ताक्षर Guarantees.
जब US citizens are abroad, कुछ financial संस्थानों may accept संयुक्त राज्य दूतावास seals, in place of the medallion हस्ताक्षर गारंटी Stamp.

The वरुण कनाडा project is the world’s पहला regional-scale भाटे समंदर वेधशाला that plugs सीधे into the अंतरजाल.

a gramophone record, commonly known as a फोनोग्राफ record ( in अमरीकी अंग्रेज़ी ), विनाइल रिकार्ड ( in सन्दर्भ to vinyl, the सामग्री सबसे commonly used बाद परिचय 1950 ), or colloquially, `` a record '', is an एनालॉग sound भंडार medium consisting of a flat disc साथ an inscribed, modulated सर्पिल groove.
The नाली usually starts near the periphery and ends near the बीच of the डिस्क.
फोनोग्राफ रिकॉर्ड are generally वर्णित by their व्यास in inches ( 12-inch, 10-inch, 7-inch, etc. ), the rotational गति at जिससे वे are निभाई ( `` 33 rpm ``, `` 78 '', `` 45 '', etc. ), their time capacity ( `` long playing '' ), उनके reproductive सटीकता, or `` fidelity `` ( `` ऊँची fidelity '', `` Orthophonic '', `` full-range '', etc. ), and the क्रमांक of channels of ऑडियो provided ( `` मोनो ``, `` स्टीरियो ``, `` quadraphonic ``, इत्यादि. ).
फोनोग्राफ रिकॉर्ड were the primary medium प्रयुक्त for music जनन लिये सबसे of the 20th सदी, replacing the फोनोग्राफ cylinder, साथ which it had co-existed, by the 1920s.
By the लेट 1980s, डिजिटल मीडिया था gained a larger market share, और the विनाइल रिकार्ड बाएँ the मुख्यधारा in 1991.
वे continue to be manufactured और बेची in the 21st सदी.
in 2008, nearly 2.9 million इकाई shipped, the सबसे in कोई साल since 1998 and the स्वरूप रै continued to धीरे regain लोकप्रियता.

Grasslands are क्षेत्रों जहाँ the vegetation is वर्चस्व by grasses ( पोएसी ), however sedge ( cyperaceae ) और rush ( juncaceae ) परिवारों can भी be मिला.
Grasslands occur naturally on सब महाद्वीपों except अंटार्कटिक.
in temperate latitudes, such as northwestern यूरोपीय और the ग्रेट मैदान और California in उत्तर अमेरिका, native grasslands are dominated by perennial गुच्छा grass प्रजाति, whereas in warmer climates सालाना प्रजाति form a वृहद component of the vegetation.
grasslands हैं मिला in सबसे ecoregions of the धरती.

हिना ( Lawsonia inermis, भी पुकारा henna पेड़ ) or हिना is a flowering संयंत्र, the sole species in the genus Lawsonia in the family Lythraceae.
the अंग्रेज़ी name `` henna '' comes इससे the अरबी ( ala-lc : ḥinnāʾ / pronounced ) or colloquially, loosely pronounced.
The name is भी used लिये डाई preparations derived from the संयंत्र, और for the आर्ट of अस्थाई गोदना आधारित on those dyes.

a पतला फिल्मी is a परत of material ranging from भिन्नों of a nanometer ( monolayer ) to several micrometers in thickness.
इलेक्ट्रॉनिक सेमीकंडक्टर डिवाइस and optical coatings are the प्रमुख applications लाभकारी इससे thin-film construction.
A परिचित अनुप्रयोग of पतला films is the household दर्पण, जिससे typically रै a thin मेटल कोटिंग on the वापस of a चादर of glass to form a reflective interface.
the process of silvering थी once commonly प्रयुक्त to produce mirrors.
A very-thin-film कोटिंग ( कम than a nanometer thick ) is प्रयुक्त to उपज two-way mirrors.
The performance of ऑप्टिकल coatings ( e.g. antireflective, or AR, coatings ) हैं typically उन्नत when the thin-film coating consists of अनेक परतों having varying thicknesses and refractive indices.
Similarly, a periodic structure of alternating पतला films of अलग materials may collectively रूप a so-called superlattice जिससे कारनामे the घटना of quantum कारावास by restricting इलेक्ट्रॉनिक phenomena to two-dimensions.
कार्य is होने किया with ferromagnetic और ferroelectric thin films लिये उपयोग as computer मेमोरी.
It is भी being applied to pharmaceuticals, via thin-film drug delivery.
thin-films हैं प्रयुक्त to उपज thin-film batteries.
Thin films हैं भी used in dye-sensitized सौर cells.
सिरेमिक पतला films are in चौड़ी उपयोग.
The अपेक्षाकृत ऊँची कठोरता और inertness of ceramic materials make this प्रकार of thin कोटिंग of interest लिये सुरक्षा of substrate सामग्री विरूद्ध corrosion, ऑक्सीकरण और wear.
in particular, the use of ऐसे coatings on कटिंग tools can extend the life of ये वस्तुएं by several आदेश of परिमाण.
Research is being done on a new क्लास of thin-film अकार्बनिक oxide materials, called amorphous heavy-metal cation multicomponent oxides, which could be प्रयुक्त to मेक पारदर्शी transistors that are inexpensive, stable, और environmentally benign.

Tropical जलवायु zones of the धरती where सब twelve महीने have औसत temperatures ऊपर 18 °C ( 64 °f ).
The tropics is a region of the धरती surrounding the equator.
It is सीमित in अक्षांश by the tropic of Cancer in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध at लगभग n और the tropic of मकर in the दक्षिणी गोलार्ध at s ; ये latitudes correspond to the axial tilt of the Earth.
the ऊष्णकटिबन्ध are also referred to as the तीव्र मण्डल और the torrid zone ( देखिए भौगोलिक मण्डल ).
The ऊष्णकटिबन्ध शामिल all the क्षेत्रों on the Earth जहाँ the सूर्य reaches a पाइंट सीधे overhead at least once दौरान the solar साल.

an airbag is a गाडी safety यंत्र.
it is an occupant restraint प्रणाली consisting of a flexible fabric लिफाफा or cushion designed to inflate rapidly दौरान an ऑटोमोबाइल collision.
इसके purpose is to cushion occupants during a crash and provide सुरक्षा to their लाशें when they strike आंतरिक objects ऐसे as the परिचालन व्हील or a खिड़की.
Modern vehicles may contain अनेक एयरबैग modules in विभिन्न side and frontal स्थितियाँ of the passenger seating positions, और sensors may तैनात एक or more airbags in an impact zone at variable rates based on the प्रकार, कोण and severity of प्रभाव ; the airbag is designed to तभी inflate in मॉडरेट to कठोर frontal crashes.
airbags हैं normally designed साथ the intention of supplementing the सुरक्षा of an occupant जो is correctly restrained साथ a seatbelt.
Most डिजाइन are inflated through pyrotechnic अर्थात् और can तभी be संचालित एकबार.
नए side-impact एयरबैग मौड्यूल consist of compressed एयर सिलेंडर कि हैं triggered in the event of a पक्ष impact vehicle impact.
the first वाणिज्यिक डिजाइन यहूद introduced in passenger ऑटोमोबाइल during the 1970s साथ सीमित कामयाबी.
Broad commercial अपनाना of airbags occurred in many बाज़ार दौरान the late 1980s and जल्दी 1990s साथ a ड्राइवर एयरबैग, and a सामने यात्री एयरबैग as खूब on कुछ गाड़ियाँ ; और अनेक आधुनिक vehicles अभी include four or more units.

China रै been the source of many inventions, including the चार ग्रेट आविष्कारों : papermaking, the कम्पास, बारूद, और मुद्रण ( दोनो woodblock and movable प्रकार ).
the सूची नीचे contains ये and अन्य inventions.
the चाइनीज invented technologies involving mechanics, hydraulics, और गणित लागू to horology, metallurgy, खगोलशास्त्र, कृषि, engineering, म्यूज़िक सिद्धान्त, craftsmanship, nautics, और warfare.
By the युद्धरत States काल ( 403–221 bc ), वे had उन्नत metallurgic प्रौद्योगिकी, सहित the धमाका furnace और cupola भट्टी, while the finery forge और puddling process यहूद known by the Han राजवंश ( 202 bc – ad 220 ).
a sophisticated आर्थिक प्रणाली in China दिया जनम to आविष्कारों such as पेपर money दौरान the सोंग Dynasty ( 960–1279 ).
The आविष्कार of gunpowder by the 10th सदी led to an सरणी of inventions such as the fire lance, जमीन मेरा, naval mine, hand तोपों, exploding cannonballs, multistage प्रक्षेपास्त्र, और rocket बम साथ aerodynamic wings and explosive payloads.
साथ the navigational सहायता of the 11th-century compass और ability to steer at high समुद्र साथ the 1st-century sternpost rudder, premodern चाइनीज sailors sailed as far as ईस्ट अफ़्रीकी और Egypt.
in water-powered clockworks, the premodern चाइनीज था used the escapement यांत्रिकी since the 8th सदी और the अंतहीन power-transmitting कड़ी ड्राइव in the 11th century.
They also made विशाल mechanical कठपुतली theaters चलित by waterwheels and carriage पहियों और wine-serving automatons चलित by चप्पू व्हील नौकाएँ.
The contemporaneous peiligang and Pengtoushan संस्कृतियों represent the oldest Neolithic संस्कृतियों of चीन and यहूद formed around 7000 BC.
कुछ of the first inventions of Neolithic, प्रागैतिहासिक चीन include semilunar और rectangular स्टोन knives, स्टोन hoes और spades, the cultivation of बाजरा, राइस and the सोयाबीन, the refinement of sericulture, the भवन of rammed earth structures साथ लाइम -plastered house floors, the creation of the कुम्हार 's wheel, the सृष्टि of pottery साथ cord-mat-basket designs, the creation of pottery tripods और pottery steamers, और the development of ceremonial बरतन और scapulimancy लिये उद्देश्य of भविष्यवाणी.
फ्रांसिस्का ब्रे argues that the domestication of the ox और buffalo during the longshan संस्कृति ( c. 3000–c. 2000 BC ) period, the अनुपस्थिति of longshan-era irrigation or high-yield फसलों, full प्रमाण of Longshan cultivation of dry-land खाद्यान्न crops जिससे दिया ऊँची yields `` तभी जब the मृदा थी carefully cultivated, '' सुझाएँ कि the हल was known at least by the longshan culture काल and explains the high agricultural उत्पादन yields which allowed the rise of Chinese civilization दौरान the शांग Dynasty ( c. 1600–c. 1050 BC ).
साथ later आविष्कारों ऐसे as the multiple-tube seed drill और भारी moldboard आयरन हल, चीन 's agricultural output could sustain a much larger जनसांख्यिकी.
For the उद्देश्य of इस list, inventions are regarded as technological firsts developed in चीन, और as such does नहीं शामिल विदेशी technologies which the चाइनीज acquired through contact, ऐसे as the पवनचक्की इससे the Middle ईस्ट or the दूरदर्शी इससे जल्दी आधुनिक Europe.
It भी करता not include technologies विकसित elsewhere और बाद invented separately by the चाइनीज, ऐसे as the odometer और chain पंप.
वैज्ञानिक, mathematic or natural discoveries, परिवर्तन in नाबालिग concepts of design or style और कलाकारी नवप्रवर्तनों can नहीं be regarded as आविष्कारों और do not appear on the list.

Globalization ( or globalisation—see spelling मतभेद ) is the process of international integration arising इससे the इंटरचेंज of संसार दृश्य, उत्पाद, ideas, और other पहलुओं of culture.
put in simple शर्तें, globalization refers to processes कि प्रचार world-wide exchanges of नेशनल and cultural संसाधन.
अग्रिम in परिवहन and दूरसंचार अवसंरचना, including the rise of the अंतरजाल, हैं प्रमुख कारकों in globalization, generating further interdependence of आर्थिक और cultural क्रियाएँ.
Though अनेक विद्वानों प्लेस the origins of वैश्वीकरण in आधुनिक टाइम्स, अन्य trace its इतिहास long पहले the यूरोपीय आयु of डिस्कवरी और voyages to the नई संसार.
कुछ भी ट्रेस the origins to the third millennium BCE.
चूंकि the beginning of the 20th सदी, the pace of वैश्वीकरण रै intensified at a rapid rate, विशेषकर दौरान the पोस्ट ठंडा War era.
The पद globalization has been in increasing उपयोग चूंकि the mid-1980s and विशेषकर चूंकि the mid-1990s.
in 2000, the International Monetary निधि ( IMF ) identified four basic aspects of वैश्वीकरण : trade और transactions, पूंजी और investment आंदोलनों, माइग्रेशन and movement of लोगों and the dissemination of ज्ञान.
Further, पर्यावरणीय चुनौतियां such as जलवायु बदलें, cross-boundary water and एयर प्रदूषण, और over-fishing of the ocean हैं linked with वैश्वीकरण.
globalizing processes affect and are प्रभावित by business और work संगठन, economics, socio-cultural संसाधन, and the प्राकृतिक पर्यावरण.

`` day-o ( The Banana नाव सोंग ) '' is a परंपरागत Jamaican mento लोक song, the best-known संस्करण of जिससे थी सुंग by हैरी belafonte और an alternate version interspersed with another jamaican folksong, हिल और Gully सवार, by dame शर्ली bassey.

संसार War I ( wwi ) was a वैश्विक war centred in यूरोपीय कि began on 28 जुलाई 1914 and lasted जबतक 11 November 1918.
it थी predominantly called the संसार War or the ग्रेट War इससे इसके occurrence जबतक the start of World War ii in 1939, and the पहला संसार War or संसार युद्ध i thereafter.
it involved सब the संसार 's ग्रेट शक्तियां, जिससे were assembled in two opposing alliances : the Allies ( based on the ट्रिपल entente of the संयुक्त Kingdom, फ़्रांस and रूस ) और the सेंट्रल Powers ( originally the ट्रिपल Alliance of Germany, austria-hungary और Italy ; लकिन, as austria–hungary had taken the अप्रिय against the agreement, इटली किया not डालें into the war ).
ये alliances were both reorganised and विस्तारित as more राष्ट्र डाला the युद्ध : इटली, जापानी and the संयुक्त States joined the allies, और the उस्मानी साम्राज्य and Bulgaria the Central शक्तियां.
Ultimately, अधिक than 70 लाख सैन्य कर्मियों, सहित 60 million europeans, यहूद mobilised in one of the largest युद्धों in इतिहास.
More than 9 million combatants were मारे, largely because of technological advancements that led to enormous increases in the lethality of हथियार बगैर corresponding improvements in सुरक्षा or गतिशीलता.
it was the fifth- deadliest विरोध in world इतिहास, subsequently paving the way लिये various political परिवर्तन, such as revolutions in अनेक of the nations शामिल.
एक of the long-term causes of the war थी the resurgence of imperialism in the विदेशी policies of the great शक्तियां of यूरोपीय.
More immediately, the हत्या of Archduke फ्रांज फर्डिनेंड of ऑस्ट्रिया, the वारिस to the सिंहासन of Austria-Hungary, on 28 जून 1914 by यूगोस्लाव राष्ट्रवादी gavrilo princip in Sarajevo triggered a diplomatic संकट जब austria-hungary subsequently वितरित an ultimatum to the Kingdom of सर्बिया.
अनेक alliances formed over the पिछला दशकों were invoked.
Within weeks, the प्रमुख शक्तियां were at युद्ध और, via उनके colonies, the conflict जल्द spread around the world.
On 28 July, the austro-hungarians fired the पहला shots of the war as तैयारी लिये the आक्रमण of Serbia.
जबकि the russians mobilised, the germans invaded न्यूट्रल बेल्जियम और Luxembourg on the way to France, providing a casus belli लिये ब्रिटेन 's घोषणा of युद्ध विरूद्ध जर्मनी.
After the जर्मनी कूच on Paris थी brought to a halt—the so-called चमत्कार of the Marne —the Western Front settled into a static battle of अपघर्षण साथ a गर्त लकीर that बदला little until 1917.
on the पूर्वी Front, the रूसी फौज was successful विरूद्ध the Austro-Hungarians, but was रोका in इसके invasion of ईस्ट prussia by the Germans.
In नवम्बर the Ottoman Empire joined the war, opening up fronts in the Caucasus, मेसोपोटामिया and the Sinai.
इटली and Bulgaria गई to युद्ध in 1915 and रोमानिया in 1916.
in Russia, the त्सार 's सरकारी collapsed in कूच 1917 and a subsequent क्रान्ति in November brought the Russians to शर्तें with the सेंट्रल शक्तियां.
बाद a 1918 जर्मनी अप्रिय along the western सामने, the allies drove back the Germans in a श्रेणी of successful offensives and अमरीकी शक्तियां began प्रवेश the trenches.
जर्मनी, जिससे had इसके अपना ट्रबल with revolutionaries, सहमत to an armistice on 11 November 1918.
the war ended in विजय लिये the allies.
कार्यक्रम on the घर fronts were as tumultuous as on the battle fronts, as the participants tried to mobilize their जनशक्ति and आर्थिक resources to लड़ो a total युद्ध.
by the end of the war, चार प्रमुख इम्पीरियल powers—the German, Russian, Austro-Hungarian and उस्मानी empires—ceased to मौजूद.
The successor राज्य of the पूर्व two lost a ग्रेट राशि of territory, जबकि the latter दो यहूद dismantled entirely.
the map of सेंट्रल यूरोपीय थी redrawn into अनेक smaller राज्य.
the League of राष्ट्र थी formed in the आशा of preventing another ऐसे conflict.
The European nationalism spawned by the युद्ध and the breakup of empires, the परखना of Germany 's शिकस्त and समस्याएं साथ the सन्धि of Versailles हैं agreed to be कारकों contributing to World War II.

अफगानिस्तान ( ; ; ), officially the इस्लामी Republic of Afghanistan, is a landlocked sovereign राज्य forming भाग of South Asia, सेंट्रल Asia, और to some extent पश्चिमी एशिया.
it रै a जनसांख्यिकी of around 30 million inhabiting an area of लगभग, making it the 42nd most populous और 41st largest nation in the world.
it is bordered by पाकिस्तानी in the south and the east, इरान in the वेस्ट, तुर्कमेनिस्तान, उज़्बेकिस्तान और ताजिकिस्तान in the उत्तर, and चीन in the दूर पूर्वोत्तर.
Afghanistan has महरूम an प्राचीन फोकल पाइंट of the Silk सड़क and इंसान माइग्रेशन.
Archaeologists have मिला evidence of human habitation from as दूर back as the मध्य paleolithic.
Urban सभ्यता may have begun in the क्षेत्रफल as जल्दी as 3,000 to 2,000 bce.
बैठे at an important geostrategic location that connects the Middle East संस्कृति साथ सेंट्रल एशिया और the Indian subcontinent, the जमीन रै महरूम home to various peoples through the ages और witnessed अनेक military campaigns, notably by Alexander the Great, Genghis खान, और in modern era पश्चिमी forces.
the जमीन also परोसा as a source from जिससे the Greco-Bactrians, kushans, Hephthalites, saffarids, Ghaznavids, ghorids, khiljis, timurids, Mughals, durranis, और others have risen to रूप major empires.
The political इतिहास of the आधुनिक state of अफगानिस्तान begins in 1709, जब the hotaki dynasty थी established in Kandahar followed by Ahmad शाह दुर्रानी 's वृद्धि to शक्ति in 1747.
in the late 19th सदी, अफगानिस्तान became a बफ़र state in the `` Great खेल `` between the अंग्रेजों and Russian empires.
following the 1919 anglo-afghan युद्ध, किंग अमानुल्ला began a European style modernization of the country but was रोका by the ultra-conservatives.
दौरान the Cold युद्ध, after the withdrawal of the British इससे neighboring India in 1947, the संयुक्त राज्य और the सोवियत Union began spreading प्रभाव in Afghanistan, which led to a bloody war between the US-backed मुजाहिदीन शक्तियां and the soviet-backed अफगान सरकारी in which over a लाख afghans खोया उनके जीवनदान.
इस थी followed by the 1990s civil war, the वृद्धि and fall of the extremist तालिबान government and the 2001–present युद्ध.
in December 2001, the United राष्ट्र सुरक्षा परिषद authorized the creation of the International Security सहायता Force ( isaf ) to सहायता maintain सुरक्षा in अफगानिस्तान और assist the करज़ई प्रशासन.
तीन दशकों of युद्ध बना Afghanistan एक of the world 's सबसे खतरनाक देशों, including the largest निर्माता of शरणार्थियों और asylum जरुरतमंदों.
जबकि the अंतरराष्ट्रीय जातियाँ is पुनर्निर्माण war-torn अफगानिस्तान, terrorist समूह such as the हक्कानी संजाल और Hezbi Islami हैं actively शामिल in a देशभर तालिबान -led उग्रवाद, जिससे includes सैंकड़ों of assassinations और suicide हमले.
according to the संयुक्त Nations, the insurgents were responsible for 80 % of civilian casualties in 2011 और 2012.
The अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध ( acw ), also ज्ञात as the युद्ध between the States or simply the सिविल युद्ध ( देखिए नामकरण ), was a सिविल war लड़ा इससे 1861 to 1865 between the United States ( the `` संघ '' or the `` North '' ) और अनेक दक्षिणी slave राज्य कि declared their secession और formed the confederate राज्य of अमेरिका ( the `` Confederacy '' or the `` South '' ).
The युद्ध था इसके उत्पत्ति in the issue of गुलामी, विशेषकर the एक्सटेंशन of slavery into the western territories.
Foreign powers किया not intervene.
After four सालो of खूनी कॉम्बैट कि बाएँ over 600,000 soldiers dead और destroyed much of the दक्षिण 's अवसंरचना, the confederacy collapsed, slavery थी abolished, and the difficult Reconstruction process of restoring नेशनल एकता और guaranteeing rights to the freed स्लेव began.
in the 1860 presidential चुनाव, Republicans, led by अब्राहम lincoln, opposed expanding गुलामी into संयुक्त राज्य ' territories.
lincoln जीती, लकिन before उसके उद्घाटन on कूच 4, 1861, सात cotton-based स्लेव राज्य formed the confederacy.
outgoing Democratic अध्यक्ष जेम्स Buchanan and the आवक republicans rejected secession as illegal.
Lincoln 's inaugural पता घोषित his administration would नहीं initiate सिविल युद्ध.
आठ बाकी स्लेव states continued to अस्वीकृत काल्स for secession.
Confederate शक्तियां जब्त numerous संघीय दुर्गों भीतर territory claimed by the confederacy.
a सलाम सम्मेलन failed to ढूँढें a सुलह, और दोनो sides prepared for युद्ध.
the confederates assumed कि यूरोपीय countries were so dependent on `` किंग कपास `` that वे would intervene ; none did और none पहचाना the new Confederate राज्य of अमेरिका.
hostilities began on April 12, 1861, when confederate शक्तियां fired upon Fort sumter, a कुंजी फोर्ट आयोजित by संघ सैनिकों in दक्षिण कैरोलिना.
lincoln पुकारा for प्रत्येक state to provide troops to retake the फोर्ट ; consequently, four अधिक स्लेव राज्य joined the Confederacy, bringing उनके total to ग्यारह.
The Union soon नियंत्रित the किनारा राज्य and स्थापित a नवल blockade कि अबोध the दक्षिणी अर्थव्यवस्था.
the पूर्वी थिएटर थी inconclusive in 1861–62.
the पतझड़ 1862 confederate अभियान into मेरीलैंड ( a Union राज्य ) ended साथ confederate रिट्रीट at the बैटल of antietam, dissuading British हस्तक्षेप.
Lincoln issued the emancipation उदघोषणा, जिससे बना समाप्ति slavery a युद्ध goal.
To the वेस्ट, by summer 1862 the संघ destroyed the Confederate river navy, तब much of their पश्चिमी armies, and the Union at Vicksburg विभाजित the confederacy in two at the मिसिसिपी River.
In 1863, Robert E. ली 's confederate incursion उत्तर ended at the बैटल of Gettysburg.
पश्चिमी सफलताओं led to ulysses S. ग्रान्ट command of सब संघ सेना in 1864.
in the पश्चिमी थिएटर, विलियम T. Sherman drove ईस्ट to कैप्चर अटलांटा and marched to the समुद्र, destroying confederate अवसंरचना along the way.
The संघ marshaled the संसाधन और जनशक्ति to आक्रमण the confederacy इससे सब दिशानिर्देश, और could afford to fight battles of अपघर्षण through the overland अभियान towards Richmond, the confederate capital.
the defending Confederate army failed, leading to Lee 's surrender to ग्रान्ट at appomattox अदालत House on April 9, 1865.
the अमरीकी सिविल War थी एक of the earliest सच्चा औद्योगिक wars.
railroads, the telegraph, steamships, और mass-produced weapons यहूद employed extensively.
the mobilization of civilian कारखानों, खानों, shipyards, बैंको, transportation और food आपूर्तियाँ सब foreshadowed World War I.
it remains the deadliest युद्ध in अमरीकी इतिहास, resulting in the मौतों of an अनुमानित 750,000 सैनिको और an undetermined क्रमांक of civilian casualties.
Historian John Huddleston estimates the मौत टोल at टेन प्रतिशत of all उत्तरी males 20–45 years old, and 30 प्रतिशत of सब Southern white males aged 18–40.
लागत of goods sold ( cogs ) refer to the inventory costs of those goods a कारोबार रै sold दौरान a particular काल.
लागत हैं संबद्ध with particular goods using one of अनेक formulas, including specific identification, first-in first-out ( FIFO ), or औसत लागत.
लागत शामिल सब costs of खरीदें, लागत of conversion and other costs incurred in bringing the inventories to उनके उपस्थित स्थान and कंडीशन.
लागत of goods made by the कारोबार शामिल material, मजदूर, and आबंटित ओवरहेड.
the लागत of those goods नहीं yet बेची are deferred as लागत of inventory until the inventory is बेची or लिखा bas in value.

A confectionery स्टोर ( more commonly referred to as a मीठी shop in the United Kingdom, a कैंडी स्टोर in the उत्तर America, or a lolly दूकान in Australia ) बिकता confectionery और is प्रायः targeted to children.
सबसे confectionery स्टोर्स हैं filled साथ an assortment of मिठाई दूर larger than a पंसारी or convenience store could accommodate.
वे often offer a selection of बूढ़ा fashioned ट्रीट, and sweets इससे अलग देशों.
Very प्रायः unchanged in layout since उनके inception, confectioneries are ज्ञात लिये उनके वार्मिंग और nostalgic महसूस.
the गाँव of Pateley सेतु claims to have the oldest confectionery स्टोर in इंग्लैण्ड.

ओक्लाहोमा ( ) ( Pawnee : Uukuhuúwa, cay : Gahnawiyoˀgeh ) is a state स्तिथ in West South सेंट्रल संयुक्त राज्य.
ओक्लाहोमा is the 20th most extensive और the 28th सबसे populous of the 50 संयुक्त States.
the state 's name is निकला इससे the choctaw words okla और humma, अर्थ `` red people '', और it is ज्ञात informally by इसके nickname, The Sooner State.
Formed by the combination of Oklahoma territory और भारतीय territory on नवम्बर 16, 1907, ओक्लाहोमा was the 46th राज्य to डालें the संघ.
इसके निवासियों are ज्ञात as Oklahomans or, informally `` okies '', और its capital and largest नगर is ओक्लाहोमा नगर.
A प्रमुख निर्माता of प्राकृतिक गैस, oil, और कृषि, Oklahoma relies on an economic base of विमानन, energy, telecommunications, और जैवप्रौद्योगिकी.
It has one of the तीव्रतम growing economies in the nation, रैंकिंग among the शीर्ष states in per capita आय विकास और सकल domestic उत्पाद growth.
ओक्लाहोमा City and तुलसा serve as ओक्लाहोमा 's प्राथमिक economic anchors, with nearly दो तिहाई of oklahomans living भीतर उनके महानगर सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रों.
साथ small पहाड़ ranges, प्रेयरी, mesas, और eastern वनों, most of Oklahoma झूठ in the Great Plains और the U.S. आंतरिक हाइलैंड्स —a region विशेषकर prone to कठोर weather.
In addition to having a prevalence of English, German, स्कॉटिश, Irish और देशी American ancestry, more than 25 Native अमरीकी languages हैं बोला in ओक्लाहोमा, दूसरी only to कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
ओक्लाहोमा is located on a confluence of तीन major American सांस्कृतिक regions और historically परोसा as a रूट for cattle ड्राइव, a गंतव्य लिये दक्षिणी settlers, और a government-sanctioned territory for देशी अमेरिकी.
stacked and standing car टायर
a टायर ( or tyre ) is a ring-shaped covering that fits around a व्हील 's रिम to protect it and enable बेहतर गाडी प्रदर्शन.
Most टायर, such as those for ऑटोमोबाइल और साइकिल, provide कर्षण between the गाडी और the सड़क जबकि providing a flexible cushion कि absorbs शॉक.
the materials of आधुनिक न्यूमेटिक tires are synthetic रबर, प्राकृतिक rubber, fabric और तार, along साथ कार्बन black and अन्य रासायनिक यौगिकों.
वे consist of a tread और a body.
the tread provides कर्षण while the देह provides containment for a मात्रा of compressed air.
पहले rubber was developed, the पहला versions of tires यहूद बस bands of मेटल कि fitted around लकड़ी पहियों to prevent पहनें और tear.
Early रबर tires were ठोस ( नहीं न्यूमेटिक ).
Today, the बहुमत of tires हैं न्यूमेटिक inflatable structures, comprising a doughnut-shaped देह of cords और wires encased in rubber और generally भर with संपीडित एयर to form an inflatable cushion.
Pneumatic tires are used on अनेक प्रकार of vehicles, including cars, bicycles, motorcycles, ट्रक, earthmovers, और वायुयान.
मेटल टायर हैं स्टिल used on locomotives और railcars, और solid रबर ( or अन्य पॉलिमर ) टायर हैं still प्रयुक्त in various non-automotive applications, ऐसे as कुछ casters, कार्ट, lawnmowers, और wheelbarrows.
Dr. Joseph Warren ( जून 11, 1741 – जून 17, 1775 ) was an अमरीकी doctor who played a leading भूमिका in American patriot organizations in Boston in जल्दी days of the American Revolution, eventually सेवारत as अध्यक्ष of the क्रांतिकारी मैसाचुसेट्स प्रांतीय Congress.
Warren enlisted पॉल Revere और विलियम dawes on April 18, 1775, to छोड़ बोस्टन and स्प्रेड the alarm that the British garrison in बोस्टन थी सेटिंग आउट to रेड the town of Concord and arrest विद्रोही नेताओ John hancock और सैमुएल एडम्स.
Warren participated in the अगला day 's लड़ाइयों of lexington और concord, जिससे are commonly माना to be the opening engagements of the American Revolutionary War.
वारेन था been commissioned a प्रमुख General in the उपनिवेश 's मिलिशिया shortly before the जून 17, 1775 बैटल of बंकर हिल.
बल्कि than exercising his rank, वारेन served in the battle as a private soldier, और थी मारे in combat जब अंग्रेजों troops stormed the redoubt atop Breed 's हिल.
उसके death, immortalized in जॉन trumbull 's पेंटिंग, The मौत of सामान्य वारेन at the बैटल of बंकर 's हिल, जून 17, 1775, galvanized the rebel शक्तियां, और he रै been स्मरणीय in many place names in the संयुक्त States.
STM चित्र of self-assembled supramolecular chains of the सशुल्क semiconductor quinacridone on ग्रेफाइट.
an सशुल्क सेमीकंडक्टर is an organic सामग्री with सेमीकंडक्टर गुण, कि is, साथ an विद्युत चालकता between कि of insulators and that of धातुओं.
सिंगल molecules, छोटी कड़ी ( oligomers ) और सशुल्क polymers can be semiconductive.
semiconducting छोटी molecules ( aromatic hydrocarbons ) शामिल the polycyclic खुशबूदार यौगिकों pentacene, anthracene, और rubrene.
Polymeric organic semiconductors शामिल बहु ( 3-hexylthiophene ), बहु ( p-phenylene vinylene ), as well as polyacetylene and इसके डेरिवेटिव.
There are दो प्रमुख अतिव्यापी वर्ग of organic semiconductors.
ये हैं सशुल्क charge-transfer देवालय and विभिन्न linear-backbone conductive polymers निकला from polyacetylene.
रैखिक रीढ़ organic semiconductors शामिल polyacetylene itself and इसके derivatives polypyrrole, और polyaniline.
at तनिक locally, charge-transfer complexes प्रायः exhibit similar conduction mechanisms to अकार्बनिक semiconductors.
ऐसे mechanisms arise इससे the उपस्थिति of hole और इलेक्ट्रॉन conduction परतों अलग by a बैंड gap.
जबकि ऐसे क्लासिक mechanisms हैं महत्वपूर्ण locally, as साथ अकार्बनिक amorphous semiconductors, tunnelling, स्थानीयकृत राज्य, mobility गैप, और phonon -assisted hopping भी significantly contribute to conduction, particularly in polyacetylenes.
जैसे अकार्बनिक semiconductors, सशुल्क semiconductors can be doped.
Organic semiconductors susceptible to doping such as polyaniline ( Ormecon ) and हैं भी ज्ञात as सशुल्क धातुओं.
Typical current वाहक in सशुल्क semiconductors are holes और electrons in π-bonds.
लगभग all organic solids हैं insulators.
लकिन when उनके constituent अणुओं have π-conjugate systems, electrons can मूव via π-electron cloud overlaps, विशेषकर by hopping, tunnelling और सम्बन्धित mechanisms.
polycyclic aromatic hydrocarbons and phthalocyanine salt crystals हैं उदाहरण of this प्रकार of सशुल्क सेमीकंडक्टर.
मुख्यतः due to कम mobility, भी unpaired electrons may be stable in charge-transfer देवालय.
ऐसे unpaired electrons can फलन as वर्तमान carriers.
इस प्रकार of semiconductor is भी प्राप्त by pairing an electron दाता molecule with an electron acceptor अणु.
मादा ejaculation is the expulsion of fluid by इंसान females इससे the paraurethral नलिकाएं through and around the मादा urethra during or before an orgasm.
It is also ज्ञात colloquially as gushing or squirting, हालांकि these are considered to be अलग phenomena in कुछ research publications.

the फीफा महिलाओं 's World कप is an अंतरराष्ट्रीय संघ football प्रतियोगिता contested by the वरिष्ठ women 's नेशनल टीमों of the सदस्यों of fédération internationale de Football संघ ( फीफा ), the खेल 's वैश्विक शासी देह.
The चैंपियनशिप has महरूम awarded प्रत्येक चार years since the inaugural tournament in 1991.
जापानी won the 2011 tournament in a penalty गोलीबारी.
The वर्तमान format of the टूर्नामेंट involves 16 टीमों स्पर्धा लिये the title at venues within the मेजबान nation ( s ) over a काल of परिचय three सप्ताह ; – इस phase is often called the संसार कप फाइनल.
a qualification phase, which फिलहाल takes प्लेस over the preceding तीन years, is प्रयुक्त to determine जिससे teams qualify for the टूर्नामेंट together with the मेजबान nation ( s ).
the फीफा महिलाओं 's संसार कप is recognized as the सबसे important अंतरराष्ट्रीय competition in women 's फ़ुटबॉल और is निभाई amongst महिलाओं 's national फ़ुटबॉल टीमों of the member states of फीफा, the खेल 's वैश्विक शासी देह.
the पहला महिलाओं 's संसार Cup tournament, named the Women 's World Championship, थी held in 1991, sixty-one सालो after the मेन 's first फीफा संसार Cup tournament in 1930.
The छह संसार कप tournaments have been जीती by चार different national teams.
the अगला संसार Cup होगा be hosted by कनाडा in 2015.

'Son of man ' is the translation of विभिन्न Hebrew and यूनानी phrases प्रयुक्त in दोनो the यहूदी बाइबल और the नई वसीयत.
it has diverse meanings, ranging इससे a normal इंसान being to a prophesied अनन्त, divine शासक.
The Hebrew अभिव्यक्ति `` बेटे of man '' ( בן–אדם i.e. ben-'adam ) appears one सौ और सात times in the Hebrew बाइबल.
इस is the सबसे आम यहूदी निर्माण लिये the singular but is प्रयुक्त mostly in Ezekiel ( 93 times ) and 14 times elsewhere.
in thirty दो मामले the phrase appears in इंटरमीडिएट बहुवचन form `` बेटे of मेन '', i.e. इंसान beings.
as generally interpreted by यहूदियों, it denotes humankind generally.
in the koine यूनानी of the नई वसीयत, `` the बेटे of man '' is invariably used as `` ὁ υἱὸς τοὺ ἀνθρώπου '' with a definite आलेख.

In Christian उपयोग, unlike the Son of God title, which रै महरूम an अनिवार्य तत्व of Christian creeds since the Apostolic आयु, the उदघोषणा of `` यीशु as the Son of man '' has never महरूम an आलेख of faith in Christianity.

rouladen ( or Rinderroulade, singular : roulade ) is a जर्मनी meat roulade usually consisting of बेकन, प्याज, mustard and अचार wrapped in thinly sliced beef जिससे is तब पकाया.

The beef rouladen as we जान उन्हें आज have become लोकप्रिय over the पिछला सदी.

ठेठ eukaryotic कोशिका.
सेल्यूलर respiration is the set of the metabolic प्रतिक्रियाएँ और प्रक्रियाओं that लो प्लेस in the कोशिकाएं of organisms to convert biochemical उर्जा from nutrients into एडीनोसिन triphosphate ( ATP ), और तब release waste products.
the प्रतिक्रियाएँ शामिल in श्वसन are catabolic reactions, which break large अणुओं into छोटी ones, releasing उर्जा in the प्रक्रम as कमजोर so-called `` high-energy '' bonds हैं replaced by stronger bonds in the उत्पाद.
श्वसन is एक of the कुंजी तरीके a cell gains useful energy to ईंधन सेल्यूलर activity.
सेल्यूलर respiration is considered an ऊष्माक्षेपी redox प्रतिक्रिया.
the overall प्रतिक्रिया is broken into many smaller ones जब it occurs in the देह, सबसे of जिससे हैं रेडॉक्स प्रतिक्रियाएँ themselves.
हालांकि technically, सेल्यूलर respiration is a दहन प्रतिक्रिया, it clearly does नहीं resemble one when it occurs in a जीना cell.
This अंतर is because it occurs in अनेक पृथक कदम.
जबकि the overall प्रतिक्रिया is a दहन reaction, no सिंगल प्रतिक्रिया that comprises it is a combustion reaction.
nutrients कि are commonly प्रयुक्त by एनिमल and संयंत्र cells in respiration include sugar, अमीनो acids and वसीय acids, और a आम oxidizing एजेंट ( electron acceptor ) is आणविक ऑक्सीजन ( o2 ).
the energy stored in ATP ( इसके third फास्फेट समूह is weakly बंधुआ to the बाकी of the अणु and is cheaply टूटा allowing stronger bonds to रूप, thereby transferring उर्जा for use by the cell ) can तब be used to ड्राइव प्रक्रियाओं requiring उर्जा, सहित biosynthesis, locomotion or transportation of अणुओं आरपार cell झिल्लियों.

This आलेख शामिल a list of देशों in the संसार sorted by their सकल घरेलू product ( GDP ), the मार्केट value of सब final goods और services from a स्वदेश in a दिए साल.
the GDP डालर estimates प्रस्तुत यहाँ are calculated at market or government official exchange दरों.
Several economies जिससे are not माना to be देशों ( संसार, the EU, and some निर्भर territories ) are शामिल in the lists because वे appear in the स्त्रोत.
ये economies हैं नहीं क्रमित in the चार्ट यहाँ, लकिन are listed where applicable.
the figures प्रस्तुत यहाँ do not take into account मतभेद in the cost of living in अलग देशों, और the परिणाम can vary greatly from one साल to another based on fluctuations in the exchange दरों of the देश 's currency.
Such fluctuations may बदलें a देश 's रैंकिंग इससे एक साल to the अगला, भी हालांकि वे प्रायः make छोटी or no difference to the standard of जीना of its जनसांख्यिकी.
Therefore ये figures should be प्रयुक्त with सावधानी.
कुछ countries/regions may have नागरिकों जिससे हैं on औसत धनवान.
ये countries/regions could appear in this सूची as having a छोटी जीडीपी.
इस would be क्युकी the country/region सूचीबद्ध has a छोटी population, और इसलिए छोटी total economy ; the जीडीपी is गणना as the population टाइम्स the wealth प्रति capita.
comparisons of national wealth are also frequently बना on the basis of purchasing शक्ति पैरिटी ( ppp ), to समायोजन for differences in the लागत of जीना in अलग countries.
( See List of देशों by GDP ( ppp ) )
ppp largely removes the exchange रेट problem, but has its अपना drawbacks ; it करता नहीं प्रतिबिंबित the मान of आर्थिक आउटपुट in अंतरराष्ट्रीय व्यापार, और it also requires more estimation than nominal जीडीपी.
On the whole, ppp प्रति capita figures हैं अधिक narrowly स्प्रेड than nominal जीडीपी प्रति capita figures.

Lapping is a machining process, in जिससे two surfaces are मला साथ with an abrasive between them, by hand गति or by रास्ता of a machine.
This can लो two फ़ॉर्म.
the पहला प्रकार of lapping ( traditionally पुकारा पीस ), typically involves रगड़ a brittle सामग्री such as glass against a surface such as iron or कांच itself ( भी ज्ञात as the `` lap '' or पीस औजार ) साथ an अक्खड़ such as aluminum oxide, जौहरियों 's रूज, optician 's rouge, emery, सिलिकॉन carbide, diamond, etc., in between them.
इस produces microscopic conchoidal fractures as the अक्खड़ rolls about between the दो सतहों और removes material इससे both.
the अन्य रूप of lapping involves a softer material such as पिच or a ceramic for the lap, which is `` charged '' with the अक्खड़.
the lap is तब used to काटें a harder material—the workpiece.
The अक्खड़ embeds within the softer सामग्री जिससे holds it और permits it to score आरपार and cut the harder सामग्री.
Taken to a finer limit, इस will उपज a polished surface such as साथ a पॉलिशिंग cloth on an ऑटोमोबाइल, or a पॉलिशिंग cloth or polishing pitch upon glass or स्टील.
लिया to the ultimate सीमा, साथ the सहायता of सटीक interferometry और specialized पॉलिशिंग machines or skilled hand polishing, lensmakers can उपज सतहों that हैं चपटा to बेहतर than 30 nanometers.
इस is एक बीसवीं of the wavelength of लाइट from the commonly used 632.8 nm helium neon laser light source.
सतहों इस चपटा can be molecularly bonded ( optically contacted ) by bringing उन्हें together under the सही शर्तें.
( This is नहीं the same as the wringing प्रभाव of Johansson blocks, although it is similar ).

A pickup ट्रक or pick-up, प्रायः simply referred to as a पिकअप, is a लाइट motor गाडी with an open-top, rear कार्गो क्षेत्रफल ( bed ).
in उत्तर America, the पद पिकअप is used लिये light ट्रक साथ a lighter duty chassis and factory built, एकीकृत bed, as खूब as लिये coupé utility वाहनों, प्रायः आधारित on a personal car chassis, but भी प्रायः on a खास समर्पित chassi लिये ऐसे उपयोग.
Some देशों have उनके own शर्तें similar to pickup, such as ute in Australia और New जीलैंड, or bakkie in दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी.
विशाल पिकअप trucks हैं somewhat rare in यूरोपीय, जहाँ vans and लाइट lorries हैं commonly प्रयुक्त लिये similar भूमिकाएँ.
The अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य of America ( potus ) is the head of राज्य और head of सरकारी of the संयुक्त States.
the अध्यक्ष लीड the कार्यपालिका शाखा of the संघीय सरकारी and is the commander-in-chief of the United राज्य हथियारबंद शक्तियां.
आलेख II of the u.S. संविधान vests the executive शक्ति of the संयुक्त राज्य in the अध्यक्ष और charges him साथ the निष्पादन of संघीय law, alongside the responsibility of appointing संघीय कार्यपालिका, राजनयिक, regulatory, और judicial अधिकारियों, और concluding treaties साथ विदेशी powers, साथ the सलाह और consent of the Senate.
The अध्यक्ष is further सशक्त to ग्रान्ट संघीय pardons and reprieves, और to convene और adjourn either or दोनो houses of कॉंग्रेस अंतर्गत extraordinary circumstances.
Since the founding of the संयुक्त राज्य, the शक्ति of the अध्यक्ष और the संघीय government have grown substantially and प्रत्येक modern president, despite possessing no औपचारिक legislative powers परे signing or vetoing congressionally passed बिल्स, is largely जिम्मेदार लिये dictating the विधान कार्यसूची of उसके party and the foreign और domestic policy of the संयुक्त राज्य.
the president is frequently described as the सबसे powerful person in the world.
The president is indirectly निर्वाचित by the लोगों through the Electoral कॉलेज to a four-year term, and is one of तभी two nationally elected federal officers, the अन्य being the Vice अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य.
The twenty-second amendment, अपनाया in 1951, prohibits anyone इससे ever being elected to the प्रेसिडेंसी लिये a तीसरा पूरा पद.
it भी prohibits a person from being elected to the प्रेसिडेंसी अधिक than एकबार if that व्यक्ति previously था परोसा as अध्यक्ष, or एक्टिंग president, लिये अधिक than two सालो of another person 's term as president.
In all, 43 individuals have served 55 four-year terms.
on जनवरी 20, 2009, बराक Obama became the 44th and current president.
On नवम्बर 6, 2012, he was re-elected and is अनुसूचित to serve जबतक January 20, 2017.
बोतलबंद खनिज water
बोतलबंद water is पीने जल ( e.g., well water, आसुत जल, Mineral जल, or spring जल ) packaged in प्लास्टिक or glass जल bottles.
बोतलबंद जल may be carbonated or not.
आकार range इससे small सिंगल serving bottles to large carboys लिये water coolers.
मैप of the प्रमुख नदियाँ, झीलों, और टंकी in इण्डिया
मैप showing नदियाँ और बाढ़ prone areas in इण्डिया
नदियाँ of इण्डिया play an महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका in the lives of the भारतीय people.
the नदी प्रणालियों provide irrigation, potable water, cheap परिवहन, विद्युत, और the livelihoods लिये a large क्रमांक of लोगों all over the country और to rural क्षेत्रों.
इस easily explains क्यों nearly सब the प्रमुख cities of इण्डिया हैं located by the बैंको of rivers.
the नदियाँ also have an महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका in हिन्दू mythology and हैं माना पावन by सब Hindus in the country.
सात major rivers साथ with उनके numerous tributaries make up the नदी प्रणाली of इण्डिया.
Most of the नदियाँ डालना their waters into the खाड़ी of बंगाल ; however, some of the rivers जिनकी courses take उन्हें through the पश्चिमी भाग of the देश और towards the ईस्ट of the state of himachal pradesh खाली into the Arabian समुद्र.
भाग of Ladakh, northern भाग of the Aravlli range और the arid parts of the Thar मरुस्थल have inland drainage.
dr.francis बुकानन surveyed the courses of the नदियाँ of इण्डिया साथ साथ their tributaries और शाखाओं in 1810-11 ad और प्रस्तुत a minute account of it.
the shifting of the पाठ्यक्रम और bed over the सदियां is very उल्लेखनीय.
Many of the channels उल्लेखित in कि सर्वेक्षण have now become dead, सूखी or भी विलुप्त.
सब प्रमुख नदियाँ of इण्डिया originate इससे एक of the three प्रमुख watersheds :
the हिमालय और the काराकोरम ranges
विंध्य और Satpura सीमाएँ और chotanagpur पठार in सेंट्रल इण्डिया
sahyadri or पश्चिमी ghats in पश्चिमी India
The bretton वुड्स system of मौद्रिक प्रबन्धन स्थापित the rules for वाणिज्यिक and financial संबंध among the संसार 's major औद्योगिक राज्य in the mid-20th सदी.
the bretton वुड्स प्रणाली थी the पहला उदाहरण of a fully negotiated monetary अनुक्रम intended to govern मौद्रिक संबंध among independent nation-states.
तैयारी to rebuild the अंतरराष्ट्रीय economic प्रणाली as World युद्ध ii थी still raging, 730 delegates इससे सब 44 अलाइड राष्ट्र gathered at the Mount वॉशिंगटन Hotel in Bretton वुड्स, नई Hampshire, संयुक्त राज्य, लिये the संयुक्त राष्ट्र Monetary and वित्तीय Conference.
the delegates deliberated during 1–22 जुलाई 1944, and हस्ताक्षरित the Agreement on its फाइनल day.
Setting up a system of rules, institutions, and procedures to विनियमित the international मौद्रिक system, the planners at Bretton वुड्स स्थापित the International मौद्रिक निधि ( imf ) और the International बैंको लिये Reconstruction और Development ( ibrd ), which आज is भाग of the संसार बैंको समूह.
ये organizations became operational in 1945 बाद a sufficient number of देशों had ratified the अनुबंध.
the chief सुविधाएँ of the Bretton वुड्स system यहूद an obligation लिये each country to adopt a मौद्रिक नीति कि कायम the exchange rate by tying इसके करेंसी to the U.S. dollar and the क्षमता of the imf to सेतु अस्थाई imbalances of भुगतान.
On 15 अगस्त 1971, the संयुक्त राज्य unilaterally terminated convertibility of the us $ to सुनहरा.
इस brought the bretton वुड्स system to an समाप्त और saw the dollar become fiat करेंसी.
इस action, referred to as the निक्सन शॉक, निर्मित the हालात in जिससे the United राज्य डालर became a आरक्षित करेंसी प्रयुक्त by many states.
At the same समय, many फिक्स्ड मुद्राएँ ( ऐसे as gbp, लिये उदाहरण ), भी became free floating.
Ducati मोटर पकड़कर s.p.A. is an Italian company that डिजाइन और manufactures मोटरसाइकिल.
headquartered in Bologna, Italy, डुकाटी is स्वामित्व by audi through its इतालवी subsidiary लेम्बोर्गिनी.
A क्रेडिट स्कोर is a numerical expression based on a सांख्यिकीय analysis of a व्यक्ति 's क्रेडिट files, to represent the creditworthiness of कि व्यक्ति.
a क्रेडिट स्कोर is primarily आधारित on क्रेडिट रपट information typically sourced इससे क्रेडिट bureaus.
lenders, ऐसे as banks and क्रेडिट card कंपनियाँ, use credit scores to evaluate the संभावित रिस्क posed by lending money to उपभोक्ता and to mitigate losses due to bad कर्ज़.
Lenders उपयोग क्रेडिट scores to determine जो qualifies for a ऋण, at what ब्याज rate, and कया क्रेडिट हद.
Lenders भी use credit स्कोर to determine जिससे customers हैं संभावित to bring in the सबसे revenue.
The use of क्रेडिट or identity स्कोरिंग prior to authorizing access or granting credit is an क्रियान्वयन of a विश्वसनीय system.
Credit scoring is not सीमित to बैंको.
Other संगठन, such as मोबाईल phone companies, बीमे कंपनियाँ, landlords, and government विभाग employ the same तकनीकों.
क्रेडिट स्कोरिंग also has a लॉट of ओवरलैप with आंकड़ा खनन, जिससे uses अनेक similar techniques.
These तकनीकों combine हज़ारों of कारकों लकिन वे हैं अधिक or कम similar or the same.
the seven SI base इकाई and the interdependency of उनके परिभाषाएं : for उदाहरण, to निकालें the definition of the मीटर इससे the गति of लाइट, the परिभाषा of the second must be known while the ampere और candela हैं दोनो निर्भर on the definition of उर्जा जिससे in फेरे is पारिभाषित in terms of length, mass and समय.
the अंतरराष्ट्रीय प्रणाली of इकाई ( si ) defines seven इकाई of माप as a मौलिक नियत इससे जिससे सब other si इकाई हैं निकला.
These si base इकाई and their शारीरिक quantities are:
मीटर for length ( US अंग्रेज़ी : meter )
किलोग्राम लिये द्रव्यमान ( नोट : नहीं the ग्राम )
दूसरी लिये time
ampere for इलेक्ट्रिक current
केल्विन for तापमान
candela for चमकदार तीव्रता
mole लिये the amount of substance.
The SI आधार quantities form a set of mutually स्वतंत्र आयाम as required by dimensional analysis commonly employed in विज्ञान और प्रौद्योगिकी.
however, in a दिए realization of these इकाई वे may खूब be interdependent, i.e. पारिभाषित in शर्तें of प्रत्येक अन्य.
the names of si इकाई हैं written in lowercase वर्ण ( the 'degree सेल्सियस ' meets इस rule, as 'degree ' is the ईकाई, और 'celsius ' is a modifier ).
The symbols of units हैं लिखा in lowercase ( e.g. metre रै the symbol m ), except that प्रतीकों लिये units नामित बाद व्यक्तियों हैं लिखा with an आरंभिक पूंजी अक्षर ( e.g., the hertz रै the अपरकेस प्रतीक Hz ).
अनेक अन्य इकाई, ऐसे as the लीटर ( us English : लीनियर ), हैं formally नहीं part of the SI, but हैं accepted लिये उपयोग साथ si.
स्मारक Canyon
Colorado नेशनल Monument ( locally referred to as The स्मारक ) is a भाग of the National Park सेवा निकट the city of Grand Junction, Colorado.
Spectacular canyons काटें deep into sandstone और भी granite–gneiss–schist चट्टान formations, in कुछ क्षेत्रों.
इस is an क्षेत्रफल of मरुस्थल जमीन ऊँची on the Colorado पठार, साथ पिनियन and juniper forests on the plateau.
The पार्क होस्ट a चौड़ी range of वन्यजीव, सहित red-tailed hawks और golden eagles, ravens, jays, desert bighorn शीप, and coyotes.
क्रियाएँ शामिल चढ़ाई, horseback riding, road bicycling, और दर्शनीय drives ; a आगंतुक बीच on the west side contains a प्राकृतिक इतिहास संग्रहालय और तोहफा shop.
वहीँ हैं magnificent views इससे trails और the रिम चट्टान Drive, जिससे हवाएँ along the plateau.
Nearby are the किताब Cliffs, और the largest flat-topped mountain in the world, the ग्रैंड mesa.
इसके विशेषता attraction is Monument canyon, जिससे runs the चौडाई of the पार्क, और शामिल चट्टान formations ऐसे as Independence स्मारक, the चुंबन युगल, and Coke चूल्हों.
The monument शामिल 20,500 एकड़ ( 32 square मील ), much of जिससे रै महरूम recommended to कॉंग्रेस for नामांकन as wilderness.
बाएँ to right : यूटिलिटी वर्दी, ब्लू पोशाक वर्दी, Service वर्दी, और Evening पोशाक वर्दी
the वर्दी of the संयुक्त States समुद्री corps serve to distinguish marines इससे सदस्यों of other सेवाएं.
Among current uniforms in the United States हथियारबंद शक्तियां, the Marines ' uniforms have been in सेवा the longest.
the समुद्री Dress ब्लू uniform has, with few परिवर्तन, been worn in essentially इसके current form चूंकि the 19th century.
उत्तर अमरीकी टेलीफोन क्षेत्रफल codes 419 और 567 serve the उत्तरपश्चिम quadrant of the u.S. राज्य of Ohio.
the largest city परोसा by ये क्षेत्रफल codes is Toledo ( and its उपनगरों of हॉलैंड, maumee, northwood, ऑरेगॉन, ओटावा पहाड़ियाँ, perrysburg, Rossford, sylvania, swanton, Waterville, and whitehouse ).
अन्य शहरों served by these क्षेत्रफल कोड include एडीए, ashland, bellevue, bluffton, बोलिंग ग्रीन, ब्रायन, bucyrus, celina, क्लाइड, crestline, defiance, delphos, Edison, Erastus, Findlay, fostoria, fremont, galion, kenton, लीमा, Mansfield, माउंट gilead, नेपोलियन, Norwalk, Oak हार्बर, बंदरगाहों क्लिंटन, Sandusky, Shelby, st. marys, tiffin, Upper sandusky, वैन wert, Wapakoneta, wauseon, willard.
Other areas परोसा शामिल the झील erie आइलैंड्स north of बंदरगाहों Clinton and वेस्ट of Sandusky.
the main क्षेत्रफल code, 419, थी created as one of the असली area कोड in अक्तूबर 1947 ; the ओवरले area code 567 थी created on जनवरी 1, 2002.
despite the presence of टोलेडो, the राज्य 's fourth-largest city, 419 थी the पिछला of ओहियो 's असली चार area कोड to have महरूम विभाजित or overlaid.
मिकी लेरॉय gilley ( born कूच 9, 1936 ) is an अमरीकी देश म्यूज़िक सिंगर and musician.
हालांकि he प्रारंभ out गायन straight-up country और पश्चिमी material in the 1970s, he स्थानांतरित towards a more pop -friendly sound in the 1980s, bringing him further कामयाबी on not बस the country चार्ट, but the pop चार्ट as well.
among उसके biggest hits हैं `` रूम पूरा of Roses, '' `` do n't the लड़कियों All Get prettier at closing समय, '' and the रीमेक of the आत्मा hit `` स्टैंड by Me ``.
he is भी the cousin of Jerry ली लुईस, कार्ल mcvoy, Jim gilley और jimmy swaggart.
according to the संघीय Aviation Administration, gilley is a licensed पायलट, जो holds an instrument दरजा with वाणिज्यिक पायलट privileges for multi-engine airplanes, as खूब as private pilot privileges लिये सिंगल इंजन वायुयान.
the सितंबर 11 हमले ( also referred to as September 11, September 11th, or 9/11 ) यहूद a series of चार समन्वित terrorist attacks शुभारम्भ by the Islamic आतंकवादी समूह al-Qaeda upon the संयुक्त States in New यॉर्क नगर and the वॉशिंगटन, D.C. area on सितंबर 11, 2001.
Four यात्री airliners यहूद hijacked by 19 al-qaeda आतंकवादी so वे could be flown into इमारतें in suicide हमले.
दो of those planes, American Airlines उड़ान 11 और संयुक्त एयरलाइंस उड़ान 175, यहूद crashed into the North और दक्षिण मीनारें, respectively, of the संसार Trade बीच जटिल in New York नगर.
भीतर दो घंटों, दोनो मीनारें collapsed साथ debris and the resulting फ़ायर causing partial or पूरा पतन of सब अन्य इमारतें in the wtc जटिल, as खूब as प्रमुख क्षति to टेन अन्य विशाल surrounding structures.
a third plane, American Airlines Flight 77, was क्रैश into the प्रस्तुतीकरण ( the मुख्यालय of the संयुक्त राज्य Department of Defense ), अग्रणी to a आंशिक collapse in इसके पश्चिमी पक्ष.
the चौथी प्लेन, संयुक्त Airlines उड़ान 93, थी targeted at the संयुक्त States कैपिटल in वॉशिंगटन, D.C., but crashed into a फ़ील्ड निकट shanksville, Pennsylvania, बाद इसके यात्री tried to overcome the hijackers.
In कुल, almost 3,000 लोगों died in the attacks, सहित the 227 नागरिकों and 19 hijackers सवार the four planes.
Suspicion quickly fell on al-qaeda.
Although the समूह 's नेता, ओसामा बिन लादेन, initially अस्वीकृत कोई involvement, in 2004 he claimed जिम्मेदारी for the हमले.
al-qaeda and bin Laden cited U.S. support of Israel, the उपस्थिति of u.S. सैनिकों in सऊदी अरब, और प्रतिबंधों against इराकी as motives लिये the attacks.
The United States responded to the हमले by शुभारंभ the युद्ध on आतंक और invading अफगानिस्तान to depose the तालिबान, जिससे had harbored al-qaeda.
Many देशों strengthened their anti-terrorism legislation और expanded विधि enforcement powers.
Having evaded कैप्चर लिये सालो, bin लादेन was स्तिथ और मारे by u.S. forces in may 2011.
the destruction of the Twin Towers और अन्य गुण caused गंभीर damage to the अर्थव्यवस्था of निम्नतर मैनहटन and had a significant effect on वैश्विक बाज़ार.
Cleanup of the संसार व्यापार बीच site was completed in May 2002, और the प्रस्तुतीकरण was repaired भीतर a साल.
numerous memorials have महरूम constructed, including the नेशनल September 11 मेमोरियल & संग्रहालय in नई यॉर्क, the प्रस्तुतीकरण मेमोरियल, and the उड़ान 93 नेशनल मेमोरियल in Pennsylvania.

in the United States, Social सुरक्षा refers to the old-age, Survivors, and विकलांगता Insurance ( oasdi ) संघीय program.
the original सोशल सुरक्षा अधिनियम ( 1935 ) and the वर्तमान संस्करण of the अधिनियम, as amended, encompass several सोशल welfare and social बीमे कार्यक्रम.
Social सुरक्षा is primarily वित्तपोषित through dedicated payroll कर पुकारा संघीय बीमे Contributions Act tax ( fica ).
कर जमा are formally entrusted to the Federal old-age and survivors बीमे विश्वास Fund, the Federal Disability बीमे विश्वास निधि, the संघीय हॉस्पिटल Insurance विश्वास Fund, or the Federal Supplementary Medical बीमे विश्वास निधि which comprise the सोशल Security Trust Fund.
Upward redistribution of आय is जिम्मेदार for परिचय 43 % of the प्रक्षिप्त सोशल Security shortfall over the अगला 75 years.
according to economist मार्टिन feldstein, the combined बिता for सब social बीमे programs in 2003 constituted 37 % of government व्यय और 7 % of the gross घरेलू उत्पाद.
सोशल सुरक्षा is currently अनुमानित to keep roughly 40 percent of सब अमेरिकी आयु 65 or पुरानी out of poverty.
the Social सुरक्षा प्रशासन is headquartered in Woodlawn, Maryland, just वेस्ट of बाल्टीमोर.
