चार्ल्स John huffam डिकेंस ( ; 7 February 1812 – 9 जून 1870 ) थी an English writer and social आलोचक.
he निर्मित some of the world 's सबसे यादगार fictional वर्ण और is generally regarded as the महानतम उपन्यासकार of the Victorian period.
दौरान his जीवन, उसके works enjoyed unprecedented कीर्ति, और by the बीसवीं century his literary genius was broadly acknowledged by आलोचकों and विद्वानों.
उसके novels और short कहानियां continue to be widely लोकप्रिय.
born in Portsmouth, इंग्लैण्ड, Dickens left स्कूल to work in a फैक्टरी बाद his पिता was thrown into कर्जदार ' prison.
हालांकि he had छोटी औपचारिक education, उसके जल्दी impoverishment drove him to सफल.
Over उसके career he संपादित a साप्ताहिक journal for 20 years, wrote 15 novels, 5 novellas और सैंकड़ों of short stories और non-fiction आलेख, lectured and performed extensively, थी an indefatigable letter लेखक, और campaigned vigorously लिये children 's अधिकारों, शिक्षा, और other social reforms.
डिकेंस sprang to कीर्ति with the 1836 सीरियल publication of The pickwick Papers.
भीतर a few सालो he था become an international साहित्यिक हस्ती, प्रसिद्ध लिये उसके ह्यूमर, satire, and keen अवलोकन of character and समाज.
उसके novels, सबसे प्रकाशित in मासिक or weekly instalments, pioneered the सीरियल प्रकाशन of कथा fiction, which became the प्रबल विक्टोरियन विधि लिये अनोखा publication.
the किस्त स्वरूप अनुमत डिकेंस to evaluate उसके audience 's प्रतिक्रिया, और he प्रायः परिवर्धित his प्लाट and character development आधारित on ऐसे प्रतिक्रिया.
लिये example, जब उसके wife 's chiropodist expressed तकलीफ at the रास्ता Miss mowcher in दाउद कॉपरफील्ड लगा to reflect उसके disabilities, डिकेंस went on to improve the अक्षर साथ धनात्मक lineaments.
fagin in ओलिवर Twist जाहिर mirrors the प्रसिद्ध बाड़ Ikey सुलेमान ; उसके कैरीकेचर of Leigh हंट in the फिगर of mr skimpole in Bleak House was likewise toned bas on सलाह from some of उसके मित्रों, as वे पढ़ा एपीसोड.
In the same novel, दोनो लॉरेंस Boythorne और मूनी the beadle हैं drawn इससे real life – boythorne from वाल्टर Savage landor और मूनी इससे 'Looney ', a beadle at salisbury Square.
His भूखंड यहूद carefully constructed, और Dickens प्रायः wove in तत्व from topical कार्यक्रम into उसके narratives.
masses of the अनपढ़ ग़रीब chipped in ha'pennies to have प्रत्येक नई monthly एपीसोड पढ़ा to उन्हें, opening up और प्रेरणादायी a नई class of readers.
डिकेंस थी regarded as the literary colossus of his age.
His 1843 novella, A Christmas कैरोल, is एक of the most influential works कभी लिखा, और it remains लोकप्रिय and continues to inspire adaptations in प्रत्येक artistic genre.
उसके रचनात्मक genius has महरूम praised by fellow writers—from Leo टालस्टाय to G. K. चेस्टरटन and George Orwell —for इसके realism, comedy, गद्य style, unique characterisations, और सोशल criticism.
On the अन्य हाथ Oscar वाइल्ड, हेनरी James और वर्जिनिया Woolf complained of a कमी of मनोवैज्ञानिक गहराई, ढीला writing, और a vein of saccharine sentimentalism.

the civil अधिकारों गति थी a श्रेणी of विश्वव्यापी राजनैतिक movements for equality पहले the विधि that peaked in the 1960s.
in अनेक situations it took the form of अभियान of civil प्रतिरोध aimed at achieving बदलें by nonviolent forms of resistance.
in कुछ परिस्थितियों it was accompanied, or followed, by civil unrest and armed rebellion.
The process was long और tenuous in many देशों, और अनेक of ये movements did नहीं fully achieve उनके goals हालांकि, the प्रयत्न of ये आंदोलनों किया सीसे to सुधार in the विधिक rights of previously दलित groups of people.
the प्रमुख aim of the civil rights movement शामिल, and शामिल, ensuring that the rights of सब लोगों are बराबर सुरक्षित by the विधि, including the अधिकारों of minorities.
सिविल rights आंदोलनों ranging from the global lgbt अधिकारों movement to the global महिलाओं 's अधिकारों गति to various racial अल्पसंख्यक rights movements around the world continue.

नई ऑरलियन्स ( or, locally or ; ) is a प्रमुख संयुक्त राज्य port and the largest city और महानगर area in the राज्य of louisiana.
The जनसांख्यिकी of the नगर थी 343,829 as of the 2010 u.S. Census.
The नई Orleans महानगर area ( नई Orleans–Metairie–Kenner महानगर सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रफल ) had a population of 1,167,764 in 2010 and was the 46th largest in the संयुक्त राज्य.
the नई orleans–metairie–bogalusa संयुक्त सांख्यिकीय Area, a larger व्यापार क्षेत्रफल, था a 2010 population of 1,214,932.
the नगर is named बाद orléans, a city located on the loire नदी in Centre, फ़्रांस, and is खूब known for इसके पृथक French क्रियोल architecture, as well as its cross-cultural और multilingual heritage.

The United राज्य presidential election of 1968 was the 46th quadrennial अध्यक्षीय election, held on Tuesday, नवम्बर 5, 1968.
the Republican nominee, former vice-president Richard निक्सन, जीती the चुनाव over the लोकतांत्रिक nominee, incumbent Vice-President ह्यूबर्ट Humphrey.
Nixon भागा on a अभियान कि promised to restore law और अनुक्रम to the nation 's cities, फटा by दंगे and crime.
विश्लेषकों have argued the चुनाव of 1968 is a realigning election as it permanently disrupted the नई सौदे गठबन्धन that had वर्चस्व presidential politics लिये 36 years.
coming चार सालो after डेमोक्रेट lyndon B. जॉनसन won in a historic landslide, the चुनाव देखी the लाज़िम अध्यक्ष मजबूर out of the रेस and a Republican निर्वाचित लिये the first समय in बारह सालो.
It थी a wrenching national अनुभव, conducted during a year of हिंसा कि शामिल the हत्या of civil अधिकारों नेता Martin लूथर किंग, Jr., and subsequent race riots आरपार the nation, the assasination of Democratic अध्यक्षीय candidate रॉबर्ट F. Kennedy, फैली विपक्ष to the वियतनाम War across university campuses, and violent confrontations between पुलिस और anti-war प्रदर्शनकारियों at the 1968 Democratic नेशनल सम्मेलन as the Democratic party split again and again.
the election प्रदर्शित the strongest third पार्टी effort चूंकि 1912 by पूर्व अलबामा राज्यपाल George Wallace, a डेमोक्रेट.
क्युकी वालेस 's campaign opposed संघीय intervention in the दक्षिण to end स्कूल segregation, he carried the गहन South and भागा खूब in जातीय industrial districts in the उत्तर.
इस was the पिछला चुनाव in जिससे नई York had the सबसे votes in the electoral college ( 43 votes ).
बाद the 1970 census, कैलिफ़ोर्निया gained the सबसे चुनावी votes and has remained the सबसे populous राज्य since तब.
इस is the latest election where a presidential ticket won बगैर carrying the वाइस अध्यक्षीय candidate 's home state.

कर्ट डोनाल्ड कोबेन ( फ़रवरी 20, 1967 – अप्रैल 5, 1994 ) थी an अमरीकी संगीतकार और कलाकार, best known as the सीसे singer, guitarist और प्राथमिक songwriter of the grunge बैंड निर्वाण.
कोबेन formed Nirvana with Krist novoselic in एबरडीन, वॉशिंगटन in 1985 and स्थापित it as भाग of the सिएटल म्यूज़िक scene, having इसके डेब्यू एल्बम Bleach released on the independent record लेबल sub पॉप in 1989.
After signing साथ प्रमुख label DGC Records, the band found breakthrough कामयाबी साथ `` खुश्बू Like Teen Spirit `` from इसके दूसरी एल्बम nevermind ( 1991 ).
Following the कामयाबी of nevermind, निर्वाण थी labeled `` the flagship band '' of पीढी X, and Cobain hailed as `` the प्रवक्ता of a पीढी ''.

A millwright is a craftsman or tradesman सगाई with the construction और मेंटेनेंस of मशीनरी.
अधिक generally in the English speaking world, जल्दी millwrights were विशेषज्ञ carpenters who erected मशीने प्रयुक्त in कृषि, खाना प्रसंस्करण and प्रसंस्करण lumber और पेपर.
in the जल्दी भाग of the Industrial क्रान्ति, उनके कौशल यहूद दबाया into service भवन the earliest संचालित वस्त्र मिलों.
आधुनिक millwrights कार्य साथ steel and अन्य सामग्री in जोड to लकडी और must प्रायः combine the कौशल of several skilled ट्रेड in order to सफलतापूर्वक fabricate industrial मशीनरी or to इकट्ठे मशीने from pre-fabricated parts.
The modern millwright जरूर भी be able to read blueprints और other schematics to सहायता him in the construction of जटिल प्रणालियों.
Millwrights हैं frequently unionized, with around 45 % unionized in the US, although अनुभवी millwrights often नियत themselves up as independent ठेकेदारों.

सोडियम azide is the inorganic यौगिक साथ the सूत्र nan3.
This colorless salt is the gas-forming घटक in अनेक car एयरबैग प्रणालियों.
it is प्रयुक्त for the preparation of अन्य azide compounds.
it is an ionic पदार्थ, is अत्यधिक soluble in water, और is बहुत acutely toxic.
Double रेनबो और supernumerary rainbows on the अंदर of the प्राथमिक चाप.
The छाया of the फ़ोटोग्राफ़र 's सिर on the नीचे marks the centre of the रेनबो वृत्त ( antisolar point ).
A rainbow is an ऑप्टिकल और meteorological phenomenon that is caused by reflection of light in water droplets in the धरती 's माहौल, resulting in a वर्णक्रम of लाइट appearing in the sky.
it takes the रूप of a multicoloured arc.
rainbows caused by धूप सदा appear in the section of sky सीधे विपरीत the सूर्य.
In a `` प्राथमिक rainbow '', the चाप shows red on the outer part और बैंगनी on the inner side.
इस रेनबो is caused by light being refracted जबकि entering a droplet of water, तब reflected inside on the वापस of the droplet और refracted again जब leaving it.
In a दोगुना रेनबो, a second arc is seen बाहर the प्राथमिक चाप, and रै the order of its colours reversed, red facing toward the other एक, in both rainbows.
This second रेनबो is caused by लाइट reflecting twice inside water droplets.
The Conservative पार्टी, officially the Conservative और यूनियनिस्ट Party and colloquially referred to as the tory पार्टी or the Tories, is a centre-right राजनैतिक पार्टी in the United Kingdom कि espouses the तत्त्वज्ञान of कोसा and British unionism.
it is the largest राजनैतिक party in the संयुक्त Kingdom, being the largest single पार्टी in the हाउस of कॉमन्स with 303 mps, the largest party in local government साथ 9,391 पार्षदों, और the largest अंग्रेजों party in the European पार्लियामेंट साथ 25 meps.
it governs in गठबन्धन साथ the उदार Democrats, साथ पार्टी leader David Cameron as Prime मंत्री.
the रूढ़िवादी Party थी संस्थापित in 1834, and थी one of two dominant पार्टियों in the 19th सदी, साथ साथ the Liberal पार्टी.
It बदला its नाम to the रूढ़िवादी and Unionist पार्टी in 1912 after विलय साथ the Liberal Unionist पार्टी, हालांकि that नाम is rarely used और it is generally referred to as simply the रूढ़िवादी पार्टी.
In the 1920s, the Liberal vote greatly diminished और the श्रमिक पार्टी became the conservatives ' प्रमुख विरोधियों.
Conservative प्रधान मंत्रियों led सरकारें लिये 57 सालो of the 20th सदी, सहित विंस्टन Churchill ( 1940–45, 1951–55 ) और मार्गरेट थैचर ( 1979–90 ).
Thatcher 's tenure led to wide-ranging आर्थिक उदारीकरण और देखी the conservatives become the most eurosceptic of the three प्रमुख parties.
the party was लौटे to सरकारी in गठबन्धन, having विफल to जीत a बहुमत, in 2010 अंतर्गत the अधिक `` उदार '' leadership of David cameron.
In the यूरोपीय पार्लियामेंट, the Conservatives हैं the largest British पार्टी साथ 25 meps, जो sit साथ the नरम eurosceptic यूरोपीय conservatives और reformists ( ECR ) parliamentary group, while the पार्टी itself is a सदस्य of the Alliance of यूरोपीय Conservatives और reformists ( aecr ) europarty.
They हैं the third-largest party in the स्कॉटिश पार्लियामेंट और second-largest in the वेल्श सभा.
वे were formally allied to the ulster यूनियनिस्ट Party ( uup ) as part of the ulster conservatives और unionists arrangement, साथ the uup currently participating in the five-party उत्तरी आयरलैंड Executive.

The Centers लिये बीमारी कंट्रोल and Prevention ( सीडीसी ) is a United राज्य संघीय एजेंसी अंतर्गत the विभाग of स्वास्थ्य and इंसान Services headquartered in Druid पहाड़ियाँ, unincorporated dekalb County, जॉर्जिया, in Greater अटलांटा.
It works to protect public health और safety by providing सूचना to enhance स्वास्थ्य निर्णय, और it promotes health through partnerships with state health departments और अन्य संगठन.
the सीडीसी फ़ोकस national ध्यान on developing और applying disease prevention and कंट्रोल ( especially संक्रामक diseases और foodborne pathogens और अन्य सूक्ष्मजैविक infections ), environmental health, occupational सुरक्षा and health, स्वास्थ्य promotion, injury रोकथाम और शिक्षा क्रियाएँ designed to improve the स्वास्थ्य of the लोगों of the United राज्य.
the CDC is the संयुक्त States ' नेशनल पब्लिक स्वास्थ्य संस्थान and is a founding member of the अंतरराष्ट्रीय संघ of नेशनल पब्लिक Health Institutes.
Earthquake भविष्यवाणी `` is प्रायः defined as the specification of the समय, location, and परिमाण of a future भूकंप भीतर stated हद '', and particularly of `` the next strong भूकंप to occur in a प्रदेश. ''
इस can be विशिष्ट from भूकंप forecasting, जिससे is the probabilistic assessment of सामान्य भूकंप जोखिम, including the आवृत्ति और magnitude of damaging earthquakes, in a दिए area over periods of years or दशकों.
इस can be further distinguished from real-time भूकंप चेतावनी प्रणालियों, जिससे, upon डिटेक्शन of a severe earthquake, can provide neighboring regions a few seconds चेतावनी of potentially significant shaking.
To be उपयोगी, an भूकंप prediction must be precise enough to वारंट the cost of increased precautions, including disruption of ordinary activities and commerce, and सामयिक पर्याप्त कि preparation can be made.
पूर्वानुमान जरूर also be विश्वसनीय, as गलत alarms और रद्द alarms हैं नहीं तभी economically costly, लकिन seriously undermine विश्वास in, and thereby the प्रभावकारिता of, कोई दयालु of चेतावनी.
साथ over 7,000 भूकंप around the संसार each year साथ a magnitude of 4.0 or वृहद, trivial कामयाबी in भूकंप prediction is easily प्राप्त using fear व्यापक पैरामीटर्स of समय, स्थान, or परिमाण.
However, such नगण्य `` successful पूर्वानुमान '' हैं नहीं उपयोगी.
Major भूकंप are often followed by रिपोर्ट्स कि वे यहूद पूर्वानुमानित, or at least anticipated, लकिन no अर्जी of a कामयाब भविष्यवाणी of a प्रमुख भूकंप has survived बंद पूछताछ.
In the 1970s there थी तीव्र आशावाद amongst वैज्ञानिकों कि कुछ विधि of predicting earthquakes might be मिला, लकिन by the 1990s continuing विफलता led many scientists to question whether it थी भी संभावित.
जबकि many वैज्ञानिकों स्टिल hold that, दिए enough संसाधन, prediction might be संभावित, अनेक अन्य maintain that भूकंप भविष्यवाणी is inherently नामुमकिन.

stührling tourbillon गति ( ).
In horology, a tourbillon ( ; `` whirlwind '' ) is an जोड to the यांत्रिकी of a देखें escapement.
विकसित around 1795 by the French-Swiss घड़ीसाज़ abraham-louis Breguet from an earlier विचार by the अंग्रेज़ी chronometer maker जॉन अर्नाल्ड, a tourbillon aims to काउंटर the प्रभाव of गम्भीरता by mounting the escapement और संतुलन व्हील in a घूर्णन पिंजरा, to negate the effect of gravity जब the timepiece ( यूँ the escapement ) is stuck in a certain position.
originally an attempt to improve सटीकता, tourbillons हैं स्टिल included in कुछ expensive आधुनिक घड़ियाँ as a विलक्षणता and demonstration of watchmaking virtuosity.
the mechanism is usually उजागर on the देखें 's फेस to दिखाएँ it बंद.
the खिड़कियाँ installer ( previously ज्ञात as Microsoft Installer ) is a तन्त्र घटक प्रयुक्त लिये the संस्थापना, मेंटेनेंस, और removal of software on आधुनिक Microsoft Windows systems.
The संस्थापना information, और often the files themselves, are packaged in संस्थापना पैकेज, loosely रिलेशनल databases संरचित as com संरचित storages and commonly ज्ञात as `` MSI files '', from उनके डिफॉल्ट file एक्सटेंशन.
खिड़कियाँ installer contains significant परिवर्तन from इसके predecessor, Setup API.
नई सुविधाएँ शामिल a जीयूआई framework and automatic पीढी of the uninstallation अनुक्रम.
खिड़कियाँ Installer is positioned as an वैकल्पिक to stand-alone executable installer frameworks ऐसे as पुरानी संस्करण of InstallShield and NSIS.
microsoft encourages तीसरा पार्टियों to उपयोग खिड़कियाँ Installer as the basis लिये संस्थापना frameworks, so कि they synchronize correctly with other installers और रखना the internal डेटाबेस of installed उत्पाद सतत.
महत्वपूर्ण सुविधाएँ such as rollback और versioning depend on a सतत आतंरिक database for विश्वसनीय आपरेशन.
furthermore, खिड़कियाँ Installer facilitates the principle of least विशेषाधिकार by performing तन्त्र installations by प्रॉक्सी लिये unprivileged users.
Four Loko is a लकीर of alcoholic पेय, originally marketed as energy drinks, sold by Phusion Projects of शिकागो, इलिनोइस.
Phusion operates as Drink Four brewing कम्पनी.
Four लोको, the company 's सबसे लोकप्रिय पेय, debuted in the संयुक्त States market in 2005.
it is अभी बेची in 48 states, and in Canada, The बहामा, बोलीविया, होंडुरास, and Europe.
the name `` चार '' is derived from the original उर्जा पेय 's चार प्रमुख संघटक : दारू, caffeine, taurine, and guarana.
चार ब्रांडेड उत्पाद have महरूम the object of विधिक, नैतिक, और स्वास्थ्य चिंताएं related to the कम्पनी allegedly विपणन उन्हें to the underaged और the purported danger of combining alcohol और caffeine.
बाद the पेय थी banned in अनेक राज्य, a उत्पाद reintroduction in दिसम्बर 2010 removed caffeine, taurine, and guarana as संघटक, और the malt beverage is no longer marketed as an energy drink.
The गर्दन of a guitar showing the नट ( in the पृष्ठभूमि, coloured श्वेत ) और पहला चार मेटल frets.
A fret is a उठाया element on the गर्दन of a stringed यंत्र.
frets प्रायः extend आरपार the पूरा width of the गर्दन.
on सबसे आधुनिक western fretted यंत्र, frets are मेटल स्ट्रिप्स inserted into the fingerboard.
On some ऐतिहासिक यंत्र और non-European instruments, frets हैं made of टुकड़े of स्ट्रिंग tied around the neck.
frets divide the गर्दन into फिक्स्ड खण्ड at intervals related to a musical फ्रेमवर्क.
On यंत्र ऐसे as guitars, प्रत्येक fret represents एक semitone in the standard western system जहाँ one octave is divided into twelve semitones.
fret is प्रायः प्रयुक्त as a क्रिया, अर्थ simply `` to दबायें bas the string पीछे a fret. ''
Fretting often refers to the frets and/or their प्रणाली of placement.
वहीँ थी खपत of दारू दोनो during और after निषेध.
The 18th amendment निषिद्ध the production, वितरण and बिक्री of alcoholic पेय in the संयुक्त राज्य और was widely supported by the American public when it went into प्रभाव in 1920.
The temperance गति था popularized the belief कि alcohol थी the major cause of most निजी and सोशल problems और निषेध थी देखी as the समाधान to the स्वदेश 's poverty, crime, हिंसा, और अन्य ills.
upon अनुसमर्थन of the amendment, the प्रसिद्ध evangelist Billy संडे कहा कि `` the slums होगा soon be only a मेमोरी.
we होगा turn our prisons into कारखानों और हमारी jails into storehouses and corncribs. ''

The metre ( मीटर in अमरीकी English ), ( SI ईकाई प्रतीक : m ; si आयाम symbol : l ), is the आधारभूत unit of लंबाई in the अंतरराष्ट्रीय System of इकाई ( SI ).
originally intended to be एक ten-millionth of the अलहदा इससे the Earth 's equator to the उत्तर Pole ( at समुद्र level ), इसके परिभाषा रै been periodically परिष्कृत to प्रतिबिंबित growing ज्ञान of metrology.

in electronics, a वैक्यूम ट्यूब, electron ट्यूब ( in North अमेरिका ), thermionic valve, ट्यूब, or वाल्व is a यंत्र controlling इलेक्ट्रिक वर्तमान through a वैक्यूम in a sealed container.
The container is often पतला transparent कांच in a roughly बेलनाकार आकार.
the सरलतम vacuum tube, the diode, is essentially an incandescent light bulb साथ an added एलेक्ट्रोड inside.
जब the बल्ब 's फिलामेंट is heated white-hot, electrons हैं `` boiled '' बंद इसके surface and into the vacuum अंदर the bulb.
If the एलेक्ट्रोड -- पुकारा a `` थाली '' or `` anode '' -- is made अधिक धनात्मक than the hot फिलामेंट, a direct current बहती through the vacuum to the electrode ( a demonstration of the एडिसन प्रभाव ).
As the वर्तमान only बहती in one direction, it makes it संभावित to बदलें an प्रत्यावर्ती current applied to the filament to direct वर्तमान.
The परिचय of a third एलेक्ट्रोड, a grid between the filament and the थाली, yields another function.
A वोल्टेज लागू to the ग्रिड नियंत्रण the वर्तमान flowing from the फिलामेंट to the plate.
यूँ, it allows the यंत्र to be used as an इलेक्ट्रॉनिक amplifier.
Vacuum tubes हैं यूँ प्रयुक्त for rectification, प्रवर्धन, switching, or समान प्रसंस्करण or सृष्टि of electrical signals.
the vast बहुमत of आधुनिक day tubes consist of a sealed container साथ a वैक्यूम inside, and essentially rely on thermionic उत्सर्जन of electrons इससे a hot फिलामेंट or a कैथोड heated by the filament.
कुछ exceptions to this हैं dealt साथ in the खण्ड परिचय gas-filled tubes below.
Vacuum tubes यहूद critical to the development of इलेक्ट्रॉनिक technology, which drove the विस्तार and व्यावसायीकरण of रेडियो प्रसारण, टेलीविज़न, रडार, ध्वनि reinforcement, ध्वनि रिकॉर्डिंग and जनन, विशाल telephone संजाल, एनालॉग and डिजिटल कंप्यूटर, and industrial process कंट्रोल.
Although कुछ अनुप्रयोग था counterparts using पहले technologies such as the spark gap transmitter or mechanical कंप्यूटर, it was the आविष्कार of the वैक्यूम tube साथ तीन electrodes ( पुकारा a ट्रायोड ) और इसके capability of electronic amplification that बना ये technologies फैली और व्यावहारिक.
in most अनुप्रयोग, solid-state devices ऐसे as transistors और अन्य सेमीकंडक्टर devices have replaced tubes.
solid-state devices last longer और हैं smaller, अधिक efficient, more reliable, and cheaper than tubes.
Tubes can be नाजुक, sometimes generate significant unwanted heat, और can take अनेक seconds—many minutes in नाजुक applications—after powering on to warm to a temperature जहाँ they perform within operational सहिष्णुता.
However, tubes स्टिल ढूँढें uses जहाँ solid-state devices have not महरूम developed, are अव्यवहारिक, or जहाँ a ट्यूब रै श्रेष्ठ प्रदर्शन, as with some devices in professional ऑडियो और high-power रेडियो ट्रांसमीटरों.
tubes are स्टिल produced for such अनुप्रयोग.
Tubes are less likely than semiconductor डिवाइस to be नष्ट by the electromagnetic पल्स उत्पादित by nuclear विस्फोट और geomagnetic storms उत्पादित by दानव सौर flares.

सर विंस्टन Leonard Spencer-Churchill, ( 30 नवम्बर 1874 – 24 January 1965 ) was a अंग्रेजों राजनेता who was the प्रधान मंत्री of the संयुक्त किंगडम इससे 1940 to 1945 और again from 1951 to 1955.
widely regarded as one of the महानतम wartime leaders of the 20th सदी, चर्चिल थी भी an अधिकारी in the अंग्रेजों फौज, a इतिहासकार, a लेखक, और an कलाकार.
He is the only अंग्रेजों प्रधान मंत्री in इतिहास to have received the नोबेल पुरस्कार in Literature, and was भी the first व्यक्ति to be बना an मानद Citizen of the संयुक्त राज्य.
चर्चिल थी born into an वैभवशाली परिवार as the grandson of the 7th ड्यूक of Marlborough.
His पिता, Lord randolph चर्चिल, was a charismatic politician जो परोसा as Chancellor of the exchequer ; his माँ, jennie जेरोम, थी an अमरीकी socialite.
as a यंग फौज अधिकारी, he saw action in British इण्डिया, the Sudan, and the दूसरी बोअर War.
he gained कीर्ति as a युद्ध correspondent और wrote books about उसके अभियान.
at the forefront of राजनीती लिये पचास सालो, he आयोजित many राजनैतिक और कैबिनेट positions.
Before the पहला संसार युद्ध, he परोसा as President of the Board of Trade, घर Secretary, and First Lord of the admiralty as part of the asquith Liberal government.
During the युद्ध, he continued as पहला रब of the Admiralty जबतक the disastrous Gallipoli अभियान caused उसके departure इससे सरकारी.
he तब briefly resumed क्रियाशील फौज सेवा on the पश्चिमी सामने as कमांडर of the 6th Battalion of the royal Scots Fusiliers.
He लौटे to सरकारी as मंत्री of munitions, सचिव of State for War, और Secretary of राज्य for एयर.
After the युद्ध, Churchill served as चांसलर of the exchequer in the Conservative ( Baldwin ) government of 1924–29, controversially returning the पाउंड sterling in 1925 to the gold standard at इसके pre-war पैरिटी, a move widely seen as बनाना deflationary pressure on the uk अर्थव्यवस्था.
Also controversial was his opposition to increased घर rule for इण्डिया and his प्रतिरोध to the 1936 abdication of Edward viii.
आउट of office and नीतियां `` in the wilderness '' during the 1930s, चर्चिल took the lead in चेतावनी परिचय नाजी Germany and in campaigning for rearmament.
on the outbreak of the दूसरी World War, he was again नियुक्त पहला रब of the admiralty.
following the इस्तीफा of नेविली चेम्बरलेन on 10 may 1940, Churchill became Prime मंत्री.
His steadfast refusal to consider defeat, surrender, or a सुलह सलाम helped inspire अंग्रेजों resistance, विशेषकर दौरान the मुश्किल early days of the युद्ध जब ब्रिटेन stood alone among यूरोपीय देशों in इसके क्रियाशील विपक्ष to Adolf हिटलर.
चर्चिल थी विशेषकर noted for his speeches और रेडियो प्रसारण, जिससे helped inspire the British people.
he led Britain as प्रधान मंत्री जबतक विजय over नाजी जर्मनी था been secured.
बाद the रूढ़िवादी पार्टी खोया the 1945 चुनाव, he became नेता of the विपक्ष to the श्रमिक ( Attlee ) government.
After winning the 1951 election, he again became प्रधान मंत्री, before retiring in 1955.
upon उसके मौत, एलिज़ाबेथ II granted him the honour of a राज्य अंत्येष्टि, जिससे देखी एक of the largest सभाओं of world कूटनीतिज्ञों in इतिहास.

A talent एजेंट, or बुकिंग agent, is a person who finds jobs for अभिनेताओं, लेखक, फिल्मी निर्देशकों, संगीतकारों, models, producers, professional athletes, लेखक और अन्य लोगों in विभिन्न entertainment व्यवसायों.
an एजेंट also defends, supports और promotes the ब्याज of his/her clients.
एजेंटों can नहीं उपज their own shows due to conflict of interest.

a ksa, or ज्ञान, Skills, और abilities, is a series of narrative statements that are जरूरी जब applying to संयुक्त States संघीय सरकारी जॉब openings.
ksas हैं प्रयुक्त to determine, साथ with resumes, who the best applicants are जब अनेक candidates qualify for a जॉब.
the ज्ञान, skills और abilities ( ksas ) जरुरी लिये the कामयाब प्रदर्शन of a स्थिति are contained on each जॉब रिक्ति घोषणा.
In 2009 the दफ्तर of निजी Management पूछा federal एजेंसियों to रोकें requiring job आवेदकों to भरण out the questionnaires, to be phased out भीतर a साल.
ksas are ब्रैड and focused essays परिचय one 's करियर और शैक्षणिक background कि presumably qualify one to perform the कर्तव्य of the स्थिति being लागू for.
A knowledge, कौशल, और abilities ( ksa ) is a concise essay about एक 's हुनर and expertise and सम्बन्धित experiences ( कार्य, education, स्वयंसेवी ) and accomplishments.
A series of KSA कथन हैं usually जरूरी when applying लिये most federal government और कुछ state and city सरकारी कार्य.
KSAs हैं प्रयुक्त as a गज to assess the सामर्थ्य of a prospective आवेदक in शर्तें of संभावित ability to perform the duties of the जॉब.
सबसे सरकारी भर्ती officials dekh for a short, crisp और clear ksa कि emphasizes results or accomplishments प्राप्त in पिछला work.
ksa कथन are भी known as मूल्यांकन Factors.
अन्य agencies sometimes कॉल उन्हें `` दरजा कारकों '', `` Quality Ranking कारकों '', `` Knowledge, abilities, कौशल and अन्य विशेषताएँ '', or `` जॉब Elements ''.
The name can be बस a नाम लकिन often it प्रभाव सामग्री and लंबाई of the essay.
प्रत्येक agency has its अपना regulations लकिन most of the समय the each ksa factor should be 1/2 to 11⁄2 पृष्ठों long.
the नीचे परिभाषाएं हैं पारिभाषित by the u.S. Office of कर्मियों प्रबन्धन :
ज्ञान, कौशल, और abilities ( KSAs ) - the गुण जरूरी to perform a जॉब और are generally demonstrated through qualifying सेवा, शिक्षा, or प्रशिक्षण.
Knowledge - is a body of सूचना applied directly to the प्रदर्शन of a function.
कौशल - is an observable competence to perform a learned psychomotor अधिनियम.
क्षमता - is competence to perform an observable बर्ताव or a बर्ताव कि results in an observable product.
the स्कोरिंग of KSA essays is आधारित on a स्केल of from एक to 100.
Job applicants must स्कोर above 70 to be माना लिये the स्थिति.
High scores are निकला through answering the KSA question as specifically as संभावित, providing examples from पिछला employment or training that clearly demonstrate तुम meet the योग्यता.
जब applying to federal government positions, a संघीय Resume is usually जरूरी in addition to ksa कथन.

प्रेम Always is the debut album of अमरीकी r & b duo k-ci & JoJo, released on जून 17, 1997, by MCA Records.

the duo यहूद originally a part of jodeci पहले इस album.
the एल्बम peaked at छठे on the US बिलबोर्ड 200 और also appeared on international charts.
The single `` सब My Life `` charted क्रमांक एक in अनेक देशों, और all चार of the album 's singles peaked above the शीर्ष 25 in the US hot R & B/Hip-Hop गीतों and the New जीलैंड शीर्ष 40 singles.
प्रेम सदा थी received favorably by आलोचकों, who praised the brothers ' गायन ability और the उत्पादन.
The एल्बम रै been certified तीन times प्लेटिनम by the रिकॉर्डिंग उद्योग Association of अमेरिका ( RIAA ) and सुनहरा by म्यूज़िक कनाडा and ifpi स्वीडन.

a variable-rate बंधक, adjustable-rate बंधक ( भुजा ), or ट्रैकर mortgage is a mortgage ऋण with the interest rate on the note periodically समायोजित आधारित on an index जिससे reflects the cost to the lender of उधार on the क्रेडिट बाज़ार.
the ऋण may be offered at the lender 's मानक variable चूहाe/ base रेट.
वहीँ may be a सीधा और legally-defined link to the underlying अनुक्रमणिका, लकिन जहाँ the lender offers no विशिष्ट link to the underlying मार्केट or अनुक्रमणिका the रेट can be changed at the lender 's discretion.
The term `` variable-rate बंधक '' is सबसे common बाहर the संयुक्त राज्य, whilst in the United राज्य, `` adjustable-rate बंधक '' is most आम, और implies a mortgage regulated by the संघीय सरकारी, with कैप्स on आरोप.
in many देशों, adjustable रेट mortgages हैं the norm, और in ऐसे places, may बस be referred to as mortgages.
among the सबसे आम indices are the rates on 1-year constant-maturity राजकोष ( cmt ) securities, the Cost of Funds Index ( COFI ), और the लंदन interbank Offered Rate ( LIBOR ).
A few lenders उपयोग their अपना लागत of निधि as an अनुक्रमणिका, बल्कि than using अन्य indices.
इस is किया to ensure a स्थिर हाशिया for the lender, whose own cost of funding will प्रायः be related to the index.
Consequently, भुगतान बना by the borrower may change over time साथ the बदलना ब्याज रेट ( alternatively, the पद of the loan may बदलें ).
इस is पृथक from the ग्रैजुएट payment बंधक, जिससे offers बदलना payment amounts लकिन a फिक्स्ड interest रेट.
Other forms of mortgage ऋण include the ब्याज only mortgage, the फिक्स्ड rate बंधक, the ऋणात्मक amortization बंधक, और the गुब्बारा payment mortgage.
समायोज्य rates transfer part of the interest रेट रिस्क इससे the lender to the borrower.
They can be प्रयुक्त जहाँ unpredictable ब्याज rates मेक फिक्स्ड rate लोन मुश्किल to obtain.
the borrower लाभ if the ब्याज रेट जलप्रपात but loses if the ब्याज रेट increases.
the borrower benefits इससे reduced margins to the underlying लागत of borrowing compared to fixed or capped रेट mortgages.
the हत्या of रॉबर्ट फ्रांसिस `` bobby '' कैनेडी, a संयुक्त राज्य सीनेटर और brother of assassinated अध्यक्ष जॉन Fitzgerald `` जोकर '' Kennedy, took प्लेस shortly बाद मध्यरात्रि on June 5, 1968, in Los Angeles, California, दौरान the campaign ऋतु लिये the संयुक्त States अध्यक्षीय चुनाव, 1968.

The आधुनिक आयु of कॉमिक किताबे is an अनौपचारिक name for the काल in the इतिहास of mainstream अमरीकी comic books generally माना to last from the mid-1980s जबतक present दिन.

An वैकल्पिक name लिये इस period is the अंधेरा Age of कॉमिक किताबे, due to the popularity और artistic influence of grim शीर्षक, ऐसे as and Watchmen.

Hamburger Helper is a लकीर of packaged खाना उत्पाद primarily consisting of boxed पास्ता bundled साथ a packet or पैकेट्स of powdered सॉस or seasonings.
The contents of प्रत्येक बक्सा are संयुक्त साथ browned मैदान बीफ, जल और मिल्क to create a complete dish.
the product line भी features products साथ अन्य starches such as rice or आलू बजाय of पास्ता.
it is बना by सामान्य मिलों.
हालांकि the classic boxed हैमबर्गर Helper उत्पाद तभी supply the मंड item and the सॉस packets, some varieties of the उत्पाद शामिल ground बीफ.
ये include a frozen food लकीर, जिससे features some of the brand 's क्लासिक किस्में in a पूरा meal kit form, साथ frozen मैदान beef और frozen सॉस packaged separately इससे the noodles in the same थैला.

a बौना planet is a planetary-mass ऑब्जेक्ट कि is neither a ग्रह nor a उपग्रह.
अधिक explicitly, the अंतरराष्ट्रीय खगोलीय Union ( iau ) defines a dwarf ग्रह as a celestial body in सीधा कक्षा of the Sun that is विशाल enough लिये इसके आकार to be controlled by gravitation, लकिन कि नापसंद a ग्रह रै नहीं cleared its orbital प्रदेश of अन्य वस्तुएँ.
The पद बौना planet was adopted in 2006 as part of a three-way categorization of bodies orbiting the सूर्य, brought about by an बढ़ाएँ in discoveries of trans-Neptunian objects कि rivaled Pluto in size, and आखिरकार precipitated by the डिस्कवरी of an even अधिक विशाल object, Eris.
इस classification राज्य that bodies विशाल पर्याप्त to have cleared the neighbourhood of उनके orbit हैं पारिभाषित as ग्रह, while those that are not विशाल enough to be rounded by their अपना गम्भीरता are पारिभाषित as छोटी सौर System लाशें.
बौना ग्रह आइये in between.
The exclusion of dwarf ग्रह इससे the roster of planets by the iau has महरूम both praised और criticized ; it थी कहा to be the `` right निर्णय '' by माइक Brown, who discovered and अन्य new बौना ग्रह, लकिन रै महरूम rejected by एलन Stern, जो था coined the पद dwarf ग्रह in 1990.
the iau currently recognizes पाँच बौना ग्रह in the Solar System :, प्लूटो,,, और.
However, तभी दो of these bodies, ceres और प्लूटो, have been observed in enough विवरण to demonstrate that वे fit the परिभाषा.
eris रै महरूम स्वीकृत as a बौना ग्रह क्युकी it is अधिक विशाल than Pluto.
the iau subsequently decided कि unnamed trans-neptunian वस्तुएँ साथ an निरपेक्ष magnitude brighter than +1 ( and hence a diameter of ≥838 km assuming a geometric ऐल्बीडो of ≤1 ) हैं to be नामित under the assumption that they are बौना ग्रह.
the only दो ऐसे वस्तुएँ known at the समय, Makemake और हउमेया, गई through this naming कार्यविधि and यहूद घोषित to be dwarf planets.
it is suspected कि another सौ or so known objects in the सौर प्रणाली हैं बौना ग्रह.
Estimates हैं कि up to 200 बौना ग्रह may be मिला जब the entire प्रदेश ज्ञात as the kuiper बेल्ट is छान, और that the क्रमांक may exceed 10,000 जब वस्तुएँ scattered बाहर the Kuiper belt हैं considered.
Individual खगोलशास्त्रियों recognize several of these, and in अगस्त 2011 Mike Brown प्रकाशित a list of 390 candidate objects, ranging इससे `` nearly certain '' to `` possible '' बौना ग्रह. '
Brown identifies nine ज्ञात वस्तुएँ – the five accepted by the iau प्लस,,, and – as `` वस्तुतः certain '', साथ another दो दर्जन अत्यधिक संभावित, और वहीँ are probably a सौ or so such objects in कुल.
the वर्गीकरण of लाशें in other ग्रहीय प्रणालियों with the विशेषताएँ of dwarf ग्रह has नहीं been addressed.
a डेबिट card ( भी ज्ञात as a bank कार्ड or जाँच कार्ड ) is a प्लास्टिक भुगतान कार्ड कि provides the cardholder इलेक्ट्रॉनिक access to his or her बैंको खाता ( s ) at a financial संस्था.
कुछ cards have a stored मान साथ which a भुगतान is made, while सबसे रिले a संदेश to the cardholder 's bank to withdraw funds from a payee 's designated बैंको खाता.
The कार्ड, जहाँ स्वीकृत, can be used instead of नकदी when बनाना purchases.
in some मामले, the प्राथमिक account number is assigned exclusively लिये use on the अंतरजाल और there is no physical card.
in many देशों, the उपयोग of डेबिट cards रै become so फैली that their आवाज़ रै overtaken or entirely replaced cheques and, in कुछ उदाहरण, नकदी ट्रांजेक्शन.
The development of debit ताश, नापसंद क्रेडिट ताश और चार्ज cards, रै generally been देश विशिष्ट resulting in a number of अलग systems around the संसार, which were प्रायः असंगत.
चूंकि the mid-2000s, a number of पहलों have allowed डेबिट ताश issued in एक country to be used in अन्य देशों and अनुमत उनके use लिये अंतरजाल and फोन purchases.
नापसंद क्रेडिट और charge ताश, भुगतान using a debit कार्ड are तत्काल transferred इससे the cardholder 's designated बैंको खाता, बजाय of उन्हें paying the money वापस at a बाद तिथि.
Debit cards प्रायः भी allow for तत्काल वापसी of cash, एक्टिंग as the एटीएम कार्ड लिये withdrawing नकदी.
व्यापारियों may also प्रस्ताव cashback सुविधाएं to ग्राहक, जहाँ a customer can withdraw cash along साथ उनके purchase.
francois Henri `` Jack '' lalanne ( सितंबर 26, 1914 - जनवरी 23, 2011 ) was an अमरीकी फ़िटनेस, कसरत, और nutritional expert और motivational speaker जो is sometimes called `` the गॉडफादर of फ़िटनेस '' और the `` first fitness सुपरहीरो. ''
he described खुद as being a `` sugarholic '' and a `` जंक खाना junkie '' जबतक he थी 15.
He भी था behavioral problems, लकिन `` turned उसके life around '' after listening to a public लेक्चर by Paul ब्रैग, a well-known पोषण स्पीकर.
दौरान उसके करियर, he came to believe कि the देश 's overall स्वास्थ्य depended on the health of its जनसांख्यिकी, लिखने कि `` physical culture और पोषण — is the salvation of America. ''
दशकों before health and fitness began being promoted by हस्तियाँ जैसे जेन Fonda और Richard Simmons, LaLanne थी already widely पहचाना लिये सरेआम उपदेश the health लाभ of regular कसरत and a शुभ आहार.
he प्रकाशित numerous books on fitness and hosted a फ़िटनेस टेलीविज़न दिखाएँ between 1953 और 1985.
as early as 1936, at आयु 21, he opened एक of the स्वदेश 's first फ़िटनेस gyms in ओकलैंड, कैलिफ़ोर्निया, which became a प्रोटोटाइप for दर्जनों of समान gyms using उसके name.
One of उसके 1950s television कसरत कार्यक्रम थी aimed toward women, whom he भी प्रोत्साहित to जुड़ें his स्वास्थ्य clubs.
he invented a क्रमांक of exercise machines, including leg-extension and चरखी डिवाइस.

Interstate 70 ( i-70 ) is an अंतरराज्यीय राजमार्ग in the संयुक्त राज्य कि runs इससे Interstate 15 near Cove फोर्ट, यूटा, to a पार्क और सवारी निकट Baltimore, Maryland.
it was the first अंतरराज्यीय Highway project in the संयुक्त राज्य.
i-70 लगभग traces the पाथ of u.S. रूट 40 ( और भी the old नेशनल सड़क ) ईस्ट of the रॉकी Mountains.
West of the rockies, the route of I-70 थी निकला इससे अनेक स्त्रोत.
i-70 is the पांचवां longest Interstate Highway, बाद i-90, i-80, I-40, और i-10.
The construction of I-70 in Colorado और यूटा is माना an engineering आश्चर्य as the route passes through the आइज़नहावर टनल, Glenwood canyon, और the सैन राफेल swell.
the आइज़नहावर Tunnel is the उच्चतम पाइंट साथ the अंतरराज्यीय Highway system with an उन्नयन of.
the sections of the अंतरराज्यीय in Missouri and Kansas have रखी claim to be the पहला अंतरराज्यीय in the संयुक्त राज्य.

Photo of 1999 कुल ग्रहण
As देखी from the Earth, a solar ग्रहण occurs जब the चंद्रमा passes between the सूर्य और Earth, और the चंद्रमा fully or partially blocks ( `` occults `` ) the सूर्य.
This can happen तभी at नई चंद्रमा, when the Sun and the चंद्रमा are in संयोजन as देखी from धरती in an संरेखण referred to as syzygy.
in a कुल ग्रहण, the डिस्क of the सूर्य is fully obscured by the चंद्रमा.
in आंशिक and annular eclipses तभी part of the सूर्य is obscured.
if the Moon यहूद in a perfectly circular orbit, a little करीब to the Earth, और in the वही orbital plane, वहीँ होता be कुल solar eclipses प्रत्येक सिंगल month.
however, the Moon 's orbit is inclined ( tilted ) at अधिक than 5 डिग्री to धरती 's orbit around the सूर्य ( देखिए ecliptic ) so its shadow at new चंद्रमा usually चूकें Earth.
Earth 's कक्षा is पुकारा the ecliptic plane as the Moon 's कक्षा must क्रॉस this plane in order लिये an ग्रहण ( both solar as well as चंद्र ) to occur.
in addition, the Moon 's actual कक्षा is अंडाकार, often taking it दूर पर्याप्त दूर इससे धरती कि इसके apparent size is नहीं विशाल पर्याप्त to ब्लाक the Sun totally.
the कक्षीय planes cross प्रत्येक साल at a लकीर of नोड resulting in at least दो, और up to five, सौर eclipses occurring प्रत्येक साल ; no अधिक than दो of जिससे can be कुल eclipses.
However, कुल solar eclipses हैं विरल at कोई particular स्थान क्युकी totality exists तभी along a सीमित पाथ on धरती 's सतह traced by the चंद्रमा 's shadow or umbra.
An ग्रहण is a प्राकृतिक घटना.
nevertheless, in कुछ ancient और आधुनिक cultures, solar eclipses have been attributed to अलौकिक कल्याणकारी or regarded as ख़राब शकुनों.
a total solar eclipse can be frightening to लोगों जो हैं बेखबर of इसके खगोलीय explanation, as the सूर्य seems to disappear दौरान the दिन और the sky darkens in a matter of मिनट्स.
क्युकी it is dangerous to dekh सीधे at the Sun, observers चाहिए उपयोग खास नजर protection or अप्रत्यक्ष देखने तकनीकों जब viewing a partial eclipse, or the partial phases of a कुल ग्रहण.
it is safe to दृश्य the total phase of a कुल सौर eclipse साथ the unaided eye and बगैर सुरक्षा, however.
लोगों referred to as ग्रहण chasers or umbraphiles होगा सफर to रिमोट locations to observe or गवाह predicted central सौर eclipses.
a राजनैतिक पार्टी ( from, genitive partis, `` भाग '', `` portion '' ) is a राजनैतिक संगठन कि typically seeks to influence, or entirely कंट्रोल, government नीति, usually by nominating उम्मीदवार with aligned राजनैतिक दृश्य and trying to सीट उन्हें in राजनैतिक दफ्तर.
पार्टियों participate in electoral अभियान and educational outreach or protest क्रियाएँ.
Parties प्रायः espouse an ideology or vision, expressed in a पार्टी कार्यक्रम, bolstered by a लिखा मंच with विशिष्ट goals, forming a गठबन्धन among disparate रूचि.
the mango is a मांसल stone फल belonging to the genus Mangifera, consisting of numerous तीव्र fruiting trees in the flowering संयंत्र family anacardiaceae.
The आम is native to South Asia, इससे जहाँ it रै महरूम वितरित विश्वव्यापी to become एक of the सबसे cultivated फल in the ऊष्णकटिबन्ध.
जबकि अन्य Mangifera प्रजाति ( e.g. घोड़ा आम, M. foetida ) are also grown on a more localized आधार, mangifera indica – the 'common mango ' or 'इण्डियाn आम ' – is the तभी आम पेड़ commonly cultivated in many तीव्र and उपोष्ण regions.
it is the नेशनल फल of इण्डिया, पाकिस्तानी और फिलीपीन.

संसार map showing the Tropic of कर्कट
the Tropic of कर्कट, भी referred to as the उत्तरी tropic, is the वृत्त of अक्षांश on the धरती कि marks the सबसे northerly position at which the सूर्य may appear directly ओवरहेड at इसके zenith.
इस इवेंट occurs एकबार प्रति साल, at the time of the जून solstice, when the उत्तरी गोलार्ध is tilted toward the सूर्य to इसके अधिकतम extent.
it फिलहाल ( Year 2013 ) lies at 23° 26′ 15.143′′ north of the Equator.
इसके Southern Hemisphere बंटवारा, marking the सबसे southerly position at which the सूर्य may appear directly ओवरहेड, is the Tropic of Capricorn.
These ऊष्णकटिबन्ध हैं दो of the पाँच प्रमुख उपाधि उपायों or प्रमुख वृत्त of अक्षांश कि mark मानचित्र of the धरती, besides the Arctic and अंटार्कटिक वृत्त और the equator.
the स्थितियाँ of ये circles of अक्षांश ( अन्य than the equator ) हैं लिखवाई by the झुकाव of the धरती 's axis of rotation सापेक्ष to the प्लेन of इसके orbit.
dvd-video is a उपभोक्ता video format used to स्टोर डिजिटल वीडियो on dvd discs, और is फिलहाल the dominant उपभोक्ता video स्वरूप in एशिया, उत्तर अमेरिका, यूरोपीय, और Australia.
discs using the DVD-Video specification आवश्यकता a DVD ड्राइव and an H.262/MPEG-2 भाग 2 decoder ( e.g., a DVD खिलाड़ी, or a computer DVD ड्राइव with a तन्त्र dvd खिलाड़ी ).
वाणिज्यिक dvd movies are एनकोडेड using a combination of h.262/mpeg-2 Part 2 संपीडित video and audio of varying formats ( प्रायः multi-channel स्वरुप as वर्णित below ).
Typically, the data रेट लिये dvd फिल्मों सीमाएँ from 3 Mbit/s to 9.5 mbit/s, and the बिट रेट is usually अनुकूली.
It थी पहला available लिये retail around 1997.
the dvd-video specification थी निर्मित by dvd फ़ोरम और can be प्राप्त from DVD format/logo लाइसेंसिंग निगम लिये a शुल्क of $ 5,000.
the specification is not publicly उपलब्धियाँ, because प्रत्येक सदस्य जरूर sign a non-disclosure agreement.
Certain information in the dvd किताब is मालिकाना और confidential.
in कम्प्यूटिंग और specifically Internet, a leech is एक who benefits, प्रायः deliberately, from अन्य ' सूचना or effort but does नहीं प्रस्ताव anything in वापसी, or makes तभी token offerings in an attempt to avoid होने called a leech.
In economics, इस type of बर्ताव is called `` free riding '' and is associated with the फ़्री सवार प्रॉब्लम.
Depending on कॉन्टेक्स्ट, leeching does नहीं necessarily refer to illegal use of computer resources, लकिन often instead to लालची उपयोग according to तहज़ीब : to wit, using too much of कया is freely दिए बगैर contributing a reasonable amount वापस to the जातियाँ कि provides it.
The नाम derives from the leech, an animal that झंझट रक्त and तब tries to leave unnoticed.
अन्य terms are प्रयुक्त, such as `` freeloader '', लकिन leech is the सबसे आम.

the संयुक्त States डाक सेवा ( usps ), भी known as the पोस्ट दफ्तर और u.S. Mail, is an independent एजेंसी of the संयुक्त States federal government responsible for providing postal सेवा in the संयुक्त राज्य.
it is एक of the few government एजेंसियों explicitly authorized by the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान.
the USPS traces its जड़ें to 1775 during the Second Continental Congress, where बेंजामिन Franklin थी नियुक्त the first postmaster सामान्य.
The cabinet-level पोस्ट दफ्तर Department was निर्मित in 1792 इससे फ्रैंकलिन 's operation और रूपांतरित into its वर्तमान रूप in 1971 under the Postal Reorganization अधिनियम.
The USPS employs over 574,000 workers and operates over 260,000 वाहनों.
the USPS is the ऑपरेटर of the largest vehicle बेड़े in the संसार.
the USPS is legally obligated to serve सब Americans, regardless of भूगोल, at वर्दी दाम और quality.
the USPS रै विशेष access to letter boxes चिह्नित `` U.S. मेल '' और personal letterboxes in the संयुक्त राज्य, लकिन still competes विरूद्ध निजी पैकेज डिलीवरी सेवाएं, ऐसे as UPS और fedex.
The usps has नहीं directly प्राप्त taxpayer-dollars since the जल्दी 1980s साथ the नाबालिग एक्सेप्शन of subsidies लिये लागत संबद्ध with the disabled and overseas मतदाता.
चूंकि the 2006 all-time peak मेल volume, बाद जिससे कॉंग्रेस passed the डाक Accountability and Enhancement अधिनियम ``, ( जिससे mandated $ 5.5 billion प्रति साल to be सशुल्क into an खाता to pre-fund retiree health-care, 75 years into the भविष्य, a आवश्यकता अद्वितीय among organizations और businesses in the u.S. ), आय dropped sharply due to recession-influenced घटती mail volume, prompting the डाक सेवा to dekh to other sources of revenue जबकि cutting लागत to reduce its budget deficit.
वॉशिंगटन, D.C. has महरूम the capital of the संयुक्त राज्य since 1800.
आठ अन्य शहरों have परोसा as the बैठक place लिये कॉंग्रेस और are therefore माना to have एकबार महरूम the capital of the संयुक्त States.

Princess काटें डायमंड set in a ring
The राजकुमारी cut is the दूसरी सबसे popular काटें आकार लिये ईंट, अगला to a गोलाकार brilliant.
The face-up आकार of the राजकुमारी cut is square or आयताकार और the प्रोफ़ाइल or side-on आकार is समान to कि of an inverted pyramid साथ four beveled sides.
the राजकुमारी काटें is a relatively नई डायमंड काटें, having महरूम created in the 1960s.
it रै gained in लोकप्रियता in recent सालो as a more distinctive alternative to the अधिक लोकप्रिय round brilliant cut, in जिससे the शीर्ष of डायमंड, पुकारा the क्राउन, is cut with a गोलाकार face-up आकार और the bottom, called the pavilion, is तराशा similar to a कोन.
A princess cut with the वही width as the व्यास of a round brilliant होगा weigh अधिक as it has चार corners जिससे होता वरना have महरूम cut off और rounded to form a गोलाकार brilliant.
the princess cut is sometimes referred to as a वर्गाकार परिवर्धित शानदार.
However, while displaying the same high degree of brilliance, इसके faceting style is अद्वितीय और completely अलग from that of a गोलाकार शानदार.
the राजकुमारी काटें था इसके origins in the जल्दी `` फ्रेंच '' काटें, having a step-modified `` Double-French '' or `` क्रॉस '' cut crown और a श्रेणी of अद्वितीय, chevron-shaped facets in the pavilion जिससे combine to दे a पृथक cross-shaped प्रतिबिंब जब the स्टोन is viewed directly through the table.
effectively, the राजकुमारी cut combines the high उपाधि of लाइट वापसी of a गोलाकार शानदार काटें साथ a distinctive square or rectangular shape.
the वर्गाकार राजकुमारी काटें डायमंड is usually slightly सस्ता than गोलाकार brilliant काटें ईंट of the वही carat weight because it retains परिचय 80 % of the rough डायमंड, as opposed to the गोलाकार brilliant which retains तभी परिचय 50 % of the rough.
The ability to retain अधिक क्रिस्टल weight makes इस shape popular amongst डायमंड cutters.
accredited gem appraisers ( आगा ) और अमरीकी Gem समाज प्रयोगशाला ( agsl ) और यूरोपीय Gem laboratories-usa ( EGL-USA ) are फिलहाल the only लैब्स कि ग्रेड the राजकुमारी cut for काटें.
वहीँ is no universal definition of what माप मेक an ideal princess काटें डायमंड और अनेक डायमंड manufacturers market ideal diamonds with differing facet पैटर्न और angles as `` ideal काटें ''.
In कंट्रास्ट to the agsl, आगा, and EGL-USA the Gemological संस्थान of अमेरिका ( gia ) रै stated that वहीँ is not enough industry सर्वसम्मति or अनुभवजन्य आंकड़ा to बताएँ काटें ग्रेडिंग मानकों लिये Princess काटें diamonds और to do so is at the risk of consumers जो may be धोखे by ईंट accompanied by निर्गुण आदर्श or Excellent cut ग्रेड.
the नाम `` Princess Cut '' थी originally used in कनेक्शन with another डायमंड काटें, वरना ज्ञात as the `` Profile '' cut, designed by Arpad nagy, a London कटर, in 1961.
the वही name थी बाद used और बना popular by Ygal पर्लमैन, betzalel Ambar, और Israel itzkowitz in इसराईल in 1979.
a similar काटें साथ only 49 facets, as opposed to the असली 58 facets of the राजकुमारी काटें, was बाद branded the `` quadrillion '' और initially वितरित by ambar ईंट in लॉस Angeles.
तीन years of ऑप्टिकल research yielded a वर्गाकार stone साथ faceting समान to कि of a गोलाकार शानदार काटें डायमंड.
a तुलना
the number of chevrons can affect the overall outlook of a राजकुमारी काटें डायमंड.
इस can usually be संकल्पित by the तार diagram कि is plotted in diamond ग्रेडिंग reports.
By adding more chevrons on the pavilion पक्ष of the diamond, the individual facets of the डायमंड होगा now be टूटा bas into छोटी facets.
as a परिणाम, it can दे a princess cut डायमंड a `` कुचल बर्फ '' dekh.
Vice versa, जब a princess cut diamond रै lesser chevrons, it tends to दे the diamond a chunky आउटलुक due to broader facets.
the घरेलू dog ( canis lupus familiaris ) is a subspecies of the gray wolf ( canis lupus ), a member of the कैनिडाए family of the mammalian अनुक्रम carnivora.
The पद `` domestic श्वान '' is generally used लिये दोनो domesticated और feral किस्में.
the श्वान रै been the पहला एनिमल to be domesticated और रै been the सबसे widely रखा working, शिकार, and पालतु एनिमल in human history.
The शब्द `` श्वान '' may भी mean the पुरूष of a canine प्रजाति, as opposed to the word `` कुतिया '' लिये the female of the प्रजाति.

कुत्तो ' मान to जल्दी इंसान hunter-gatherers led to उन्हें quickly बनने ubiquitous across संसार संस्कृतियों.
Dogs perform many भूमिकाएँ for people, ऐसे as शिकार, herding, pulling loads, सुरक्षा, assisting पुलिस और military, companionship, and, अधिक recently, aiding विकलांग individuals.

through this चयनात्मक प्रजनन, the श्वान has developed into hundreds of varied breeds, and shows अधिक behavioral और morphological variation than कोई अन्य जमीन स्तनधारी.

आरेख of a हस्तांतरण electron microscope
a 1973 Siemens electron सूक्ष्मदर्शी, musée des कला et métiers, पेरिस
An इलेक्ट्रॉन सूक्ष्मदर्शी ( em ) is a type of microscope कि uses an electron beam to illuminate a नमूना और उपज a magnified image.
An EM रै वृहद resolving power than a लाइट सूक्ष्मदर्शी और can खुलासा the structure of smaller objects क्युकी electrons have wavelengths परिचय 100,000 times shorter than visible light photons.
वे can achieve बेहतर than 50 pm resolution and magnifications of up to about 10,000,000x whereas ordinary, non-confocal लाइट microscopes are सीमित by diffraction to about 200 nm resolution and useful magnifications नीचे 2000x.
the इलेक्ट्रॉन microscope उपयोग electrostatic और electromagnetic lenses to कंट्रोल the electron बीम and focus it to रूप an चित्र.
ये इलेक्ट्रॉन ऑप्टिकल lenses are analogous to the glass lenses of a light optical microscope.
इलेक्ट्रॉन microscopes हैं प्रयुक्त to investigate the ultrastructure of a wide दायरा of biological and inorganic नमूनों सहित microorganisms, कोशिकाएं, विशाल अणुओं, biopsy samples, धातुओं, और crystals.
industrially, the इलेक्ट्रॉन microscope is प्रायः प्रयुक्त for quality control और विफलता विश्लेषण.
आधुनिक इलेक्ट्रॉन microscopes produce इलेक्ट्रॉन micrographs, using specialized डिजिटल cameras or फ़्रेम grabbers to कैप्चर the image.

वहीँ हैं दो main प्रकार of leg press:
The diagonal or vertical 'sled ' प्रकार leg press.

न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड और Labrador (, locally ) is the easternmost province of कनाडा.
situated in the country 's Atlantic region, it incorporates the द्वीप of न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड and मेनलैंड labrador to the northwest, with a संयुक्त area of.
In 2011, the प्रांत 's जनसांख्यिकी was 514,536.
लगभग 92 percent of the प्रांत 's जनसांख्यिकी जीवनदान on the द्वीप of Newfoundland ( सहित its associated छोटी islands ), of which more than half सजीव on the avalon प्रायद्वीप.
the province is Canada 's सबसे linguistically homogenous, साथ 97.6 % of residents रिपोर्टिंग अंग्रेज़ी ( न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड अंग्रेज़ी ) as उनके mother tongue in the 2006 जनसांख्यिकी ;.
Historically, न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड थी also घर to unique किस्में of French, and Irish, as खूब as the now-extinct Beothuk भाषा.
In labrador, लोकल dialects of Innu-aimun and inuktitut are also बोला.
न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड और labrador 's पूंजी और largest नगर, St. जॉन 's, is कनाडा 's 20th-largest जनसांख्यिकी महानगर क्षेत्रफल, और is घर to लगभग 40 प्रतिशत of the province 's जनसांख्यिकी.
St. जॉन 's is the सीट of government, घर to the हाउस of सभा of Newfoundland और labrador और the highest अदालत in the jurisdiction, the Newfoundland और labrador अदालत of Appeal.
A पूर्व उपनिवेश और डोमिनियन of the संयुक्त किंगडम, न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड and labrador became the tenth प्रांत to डालें the कनाडाई कनफेडरेशन on कूच 31, 1949, as Newfoundland.
on दिसम्बर 6, 2001, an amendment थी बना to the Constitution of कनाडा to change the प्रांत 's official name to Newfoundland और labrador.
in day-to-day वार्तालाप, however, Canadians generally स्टिल refer to the प्रांत itself as न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड and to the region on the Canadian मेनलैंड as labrador.

Roosevelt, jr. ( ; अक्तूबर 27, 1858—january 6, 1919 ) was the 26th President of the संयुक्त States ( 1901–1909 ).
He is noted लिये his समृद्ध personality, range of रूचि और उपलब्धियाँ, और उसके नेतृत्व of the Progressive गति, as खूब as उसके `` cowboy `` persona और मजबूत मर्दानगी.
He थी a नेता of the रिपब्लिकन पार्टी and संस्थापक of the first incarnation of the short-lived प्रगतिशील ( `` Bull मूस '' ) पार्टी of 1912.
पहले बनने President, he held offices at the नगर, राज्य, and federal स्तर.
रूज़वेल्ट 's achievements as a naturalist, एक्सप्लोरर, शिकारी, author, और soldier हैं as much a भाग of his fame as कोई दफ्तर he held as a politician.
Roosevelt थी 42 सालो old when sworn in as अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य in 1901, बनाना उसे the youngest president कभी ; he ताल out the youngest elected president, John F. कैनेडी, by तभी एक साल.
रूज़वेल्ट was also the first of तभी three sitting presidents to have जीती the नोबेल सलाम पुरस्कार.
the Teddy bear is नामित after उसे, despite his contempt for being पुकारा `` Teddy ''.
born into a wealthy family in नई यॉर्क नगर, Roosevelt was a sickly चाइल्ड जो suffered इससे asthma and stayed at घर studying natural history.
to overcome his शारीरिक weakness, he embraced a ज़ोरदार life.
home-schooled, he became an eager छात्र of nature.
he attended हार्वर्ड विश्वविद्यालयों, where he studied जीवविज्ञान, boxed और विकसित an ब्याज in naval affairs.
in 1881, एक साल आउट of Harvard, he was निर्वाचित to the नई यॉर्क राज्य सभा, जहाँ he became a leader of the सुधार गुट of उसके Republican पार्टी ( the `` GOP '' ).
उसके The नवल युद्ध of 1812 ( 1882 ) स्थापित his पेशेवर प्रतिष्ठा as a serious historian ; he लिखा numerous books on hunting, the बाहरी, और current राजनैतिक मुद्दे, as well as frontier इतिहास.
In 1884, his पहला बीवी और उसके mother died on the वही day.
he temporarily left राजनीती और went to the frontier, becoming a rancher in the `` Badlands '' in the dakotas.
returning to New यॉर्क नगर, he ran for महापौर in 1886, finishing third with 60,000 मत.
He बाद gained कीर्ति by लेने vigorous चार्ज of the नगर पुलिस.
at the national स्तर, he थी a नेता in सिविल सेवा सुधार.
the spanish–american War broke आउट in 1898 जबकि रूज़वेल्ट थी, effectively, कार्यशील the Department of the नेवी.
He फौरन resigned and formed the अशिष्ट Riders – a स्वयंसेवी cavalry regiment कि लड़ा in क्यूबा.
the युद्ध hero was निर्वाचित governor in 1898 और in 1900 थी nominated लिये vice अध्यक्ष.
he सफलतापूर्वक energized the gop base as a highly visible campaigner to reelect President विलियम McKinley on a मंच of ऊँची tariffs, the gold standard, imperialism, समृद्धि at घर और victory abroad.
in 1901, President विलियम mckinley थी assassinated और रूज़वेल्ट became अध्यक्ष.
He attempted to move the Republican पार्टी ( gop ) toward प्रगतिवाद, सहित विश्वास busting and increased विनियमन of व्यवसायों.
Roosevelt became the first person elected to a पद in उसके own सही in 1904 बाद having ascended to the Presidency ( from the Vice-Presidency ) upon the मौत of उसके predecessor, जीतना the largest प्रतिशत of the लोकप्रिय vote चूंकि the uncontested चुनाव of 1820.
Roosevelt coined the phrase `` वर्गाकार Deal `` to describe उसके घरेलू agenda, emphasizing कि the औसत citizen होता मिलेंगी a मेला share अंतर्गत उसके नीतियों.
as an outdoorsman and naturalist, he प्रचारित the संरक्षण गति.

A cousin is a relative with whom a व्यक्ति shares एक or more आम पूर्वज ( s ) ( other than a जनक, child/descendant, सहोदर, child/descendant of a सहोदर, or सहोदर of a parent/ancestor ).
however in common parlance, `` cousin '' normally specifically अर्थात् `` पहला cousin ''.
प्रणालियों of `` डिग्री '' और `` removals '' हैं प्रयुक्त in the English-speaking world to describe the सटीक संबंध between two cousins ( in the broad sense ) and the पूर्वज वे have in common.
विभिन्न governmental entities have स्थापित प्रणालियों लिये विधिक use that can more precisely बताएँ kinships साथ common पूर्वजो existing any number of generations in the पास्ट, though आम उपयोग प्रायः eliminates the डिग्री और removals और refers to लोगों साथ आम ancestry as बस `` distant cousins '' or `` रिश्तेदारों ''.

Three types of कोशिका प्रभाग
कोशिका प्रभाग is the प्रक्रम by which a जनक कोशिका divides into two or more बेटी कोशिकाएं.
कोशिका division usually occurs as part of a larger कोशिका साईकिल.
In eukaryotes, वहीँ are दो पृथक प्रकार of cell प्रभाग : a vegetative division, whereby each बेटी कोशिका is genetically identical to the जनक cell ( समसूत्रण ), and a reductive कोशिका division, whereby the क्रमांक of गुणसूत्रों in the daughter कोशिकाएं is reduced by हाफ, to produce haploid गैमीट ( meiosis ).
दोनो of ये कोशिका division चक्र हैं required in sexually reproducing जीवों at कुछ पाइंट in उनके जीवन cycle, and both are believed to be present in the last eukaryotic common पूर्वज Prokaryotes also undergo a vegetative cell division ज्ञात as शब्दकोष fission, जहाँ उनके genetic सामग्री is segregated बराबर into दो बेटी कोशिकाएं.
सब cell divisions, regardless of सजीव, are preceded by a single round of DNA replication.
लिये simple एककोशिकीय जीवों ऐसे as the amoeba, एक cell प्रभाग is equivalent to जनन – an entire नई सजीव is created.
on a larger scale, mitotic कोशिका प्रभाग can बनाएँ progeny इससे बहुकोशिकीय जीवों, ऐसे as पौधे कि grow इससे cuttings.
Cell division भी enables sexually reproducing organisms to develop इससे the one-celled zygote, which itself थी produced by cell division इससे गैमीट.
और बाद विकास, कोशिका प्रभाग allows लिये continual निर्माण and repair of the सजीव.
A human होने 's body अनुभवों परिचय 10,000 खरब कोशिका विभाजन in a lifetime.
कोशिका division has महरूम modeled by परिमित subdivision नियम.
The प्राथमिक concern of cell प्रभाग is the मेंटेनेंस of the असली cell 's genome.
पहले division can occur, the genomic information कि is stored in गुणसूत्रों जरूर be replicated, and the duplicated genome जरूर be अलग cleanly between कोशिकाएं.
a ग्रेट सौदे of सेल्यूलर infrastructure is involved in keeping genomic information सतत between `` generations ''.

the International Isle of man tt ( Tourist Trophy ) Race is a मोटरसाइकिल रेसिंग इवेंट आयोजित on the आइल of Man और थी for अनेक सालो the most prestigious मोटरसाइकिल रेस in the world.
the event थी part of the fim Motorcycle ग्रैंड प्रिक्स World चैंपियनशिप दौरान the period 1949–1976 पहले being transferred to the United किंगडम after सुरक्षा concerns और चलाएं by the fim as the अंग्रेजों Grand प्रिक्स लिये the 1977 ऋतु.
the Isle of Man TT दौड़ became part of the tt सूत्र 1 Championship from 1977 to 1990 to preserve the इवेंट 's रेसिंग status.
इससे 1989 the रेसिंग रै been विकसित by the Isle of man Department of Tourism as the Isle of Man tt पर्व.
The race is चलाएं in a time-trial format on public सड़कें closed for रेसिंग by the provisions of an अधिनियम of tynwald ( the पार्लियामेंट of the आइल of Man ).
the पहला रेस थी held on Tuesday 28 may 1907 और थी पुकारा the अंतरराष्ट्रीय auto-cycle पर्यटक ट्रॉफी.
The event was organised by the Auto-Cycle क्लबों over 10 गोद of the St जॉन 's Short Course of 15 मील 1,470 गज लिये road-legal touring मोटरसाइकिल with exhaust silencers, saddles, pedals और mud-guards.
the विजेता of the single-cylinder क्लास, and overall winner of the first इवेंट in 1907, was Charlie collier riding a Matchless motorcycle in a समय of 4 hours, 8 मिनट्स और 8 सेकेंड at an average रेस speed of 38.21 किमी.
The विजेता of the twin-cylinder क्लास थी rem Fowler सवारी a peugeot engined Norton in a time of 4 घंटों 21 minutes और 52 सेकेंड at an average race speed of 36.21 किमी.
the trophy presented to चार्ली collier as the winner of the 1907 आइल of man tt रेस, थी दान by the Marquis de Mouzilly st. मंगल.
It प्रदर्शित a stylised version of ओलम्पिक God hermes by giovanni da बोलोग्ना as a silver figurine astride a winged wheel.
the trophy थी similar in design to the 18 कैरेट gold montague ट्रॉफी प्रस्तुत to John नेपियर ( arrol-johnston ) as the inaugural विजेता of the Isle of man पर्यटक Trophy car रेस in 1905 अभी ज्ञात as the rac Tourist ट्रॉफी.
the Marquis de Mouzilly st. Mars ट्रॉफी is now प्रस्तुत annually to the winner of the Isle of man वरिष्ठ TT motor-cycle Race.
the 2007 Isle of man tt थी the Centenary event जिससे ran between 26 may and 8 जून 2007 and प्रदर्शित a special Re-enactment of the 1907 आइल of Man tt रेस आयोजित on the village ग्रीन next to tynwald Hill in St John 's on Monday 28 May 2007.
The vintage परेड of 100 classic motorcycles लिये the centenary Re-enactment on the असली st जॉन 's छोटी कोर्स थी flagged दूर by पूर्व संसार Motor-Cycle चैंपियन ज्यॉफ Duke.
the पहला of the भागीदार to be flagged away थी the recently restored twin-cylinder peugeot-norton ridden by Rem fowler दौरान the first आइल of man tt Race in 1907.
भी participating in the 2007 re-enactment was tt रेस competitor Guy Martin riding a 1938 triumph बाघ 100 500 cc and अन्य former TT competitors including एलन cathcart, Sammy मिलर, उपनाम Jefferies and मिक ग्रान्ट also समाप्त the re-enactment lap.

बेरोजगारी ( or joblessness ) occurs when लोगों हैं बगैर कार्य and actively seeking कार्य.
The unemployment रेट is a माप of the व्यापकता of unemployment और it is गणना as a percentage by dividing the क्रमांक of unemployed individuals by all individuals फिलहाल in the labor force.
दौरान अवधि of recession, an अर्थव्यवस्था प्रायः अनुभवों a relatively ऊँची unemployment rate.
according to अंतरराष्ट्रीय श्रमिक संगठन रपट, अधिक than 197 लाख people globally are आउट of कार्य or 6 % of the world 's workforce यहूद without a जॉब in 2012.
There remains considerable theoretical बहस regarding the कल्याणकारी, consequences and समाधान लिये बेरोजगारी.
Classical economics, New शास्त्रीय economics, और the Austrian स्कूल of अर्थशास्त्र argue that market mechanisms हैं विश्वसनीय अर्थात् of resolving unemployment.
ये theories argue विरूद्ध interventions imposed on the labor मार्केट from the outside, ऐसे as unionization, न्यूनतम मजदूरी कानून, कर, और अन्य regulations कि वे अर्जी discourage the भर्ती of मजदूर.
keynesian अर्थशास्त्र emphasizes the cyclical nature of unemployment and अनुशंसा सरकारी interventions in the अर्थव्यवस्था that it claims will reduce बेरोजगारी दौरान recessions.
This theory focuses on तूल झटके कि एकाएक reduce कुल माँग लिये goods and services and यूँ reduce demand for मजदूर.
Keynesian मॉडल recommend सरकारी interventions designed to बढ़ाएँ माँग for मजदूर ; ये can शामिल financial stimuli, सरेआम वित्तपोषित जॉब सृष्टि, and expansionist monetary नीतियों.
in addition to these व्यापक theories of unemployment, वहीँ are a few categorizations of unemployment कि हैं used to अधिक precisely model the effects of unemployment within the आर्थिक system.
the main प्रकार of बेरोजगारी शामिल संरचनात्मक unemployment which focuses on structural problems in the अर्थव्यवस्था and inefficiencies अंतर्निहित in labour बाज़ार, सहित a बेमेल between the सप्लाई और माँग of laborers साथ necessary skill sets.
संरचनात्मक arguments emphasize कल्याणकारी और solutions related to विघटनकारी technologies और वैश्वीकरण.
चर्चाएँ of frictional बेरोजगारी फ़ोकस on voluntary निर्णय to कार्य आधारित on each individuals ' valuation of their own कार्य और कैसा कि compares to वर्तमान wage दरों प्लस the time और प्रयत्न required to find a जॉब.
Causes और solutions for frictional बेरोजगारी प्रायः पता जॉब entry दहलीज and wage दरों.
Behavioral अर्थशास्त्रियों highlight individual biases in निर्णय बनाना, और प्रायः involve problems और solutions concerning स्टिकी मजदूरी and efficiency मजदूरी.
collectivism is कोई philosophic, राजनैतिक, धार्मिक, आर्थिक, or सोशल आउटलुक कि emphasizes the interdependence of प्रत्येक इंसान होने in a समाज or सभ्यता.
collectivism is a basic सांस्कृतिक तत्व that exists as the रिवर्स of व्यक्तिगत in इंसान nature ( in the वही रास्ता ऊँची कॉन्टेक्स्ट culture exists as the reverse of कम कॉन्टेक्स्ट culture ).
collectivist orientations तनाव the importance of मिलाप within सोशल समूह ( ऐसे as an `` in-group '', in what specific कॉन्टेक्स्ट it is defined ) और in some मामले, the प्रधानता of समूह goals over व्यक्तिगत लक्ष्य.
collectivists प्रायः फ़ोकस on जातियाँ, society, स्वदेश or देश.
it रै महरूम प्रयुक्त as an element in many अलग और diverse types of सरकारी and political, economic और शैक्षणिक तत्त्वज्ञान throughout history और सबसे इंसान societies in practice contain तत्व of दोनो individualism and collectivism.
Some examples of collectivist संस्कृतियों शामिल India और Japan.
Collectivism can be divided into आड़ा collectivism और लंबवत collectivism.
आड़ा collectivism तनावों सामूहिक decision-making among equal individuals, and is यूँ usually आधारित on decentralization and समतावाद.
लंबवत collectivism is आधारित on hierarchical structures of शक्ति और on moral और cultural conformity, और is therefore based on centralization और पदानुक्रम.
a सहकारी enterprise would be an example of horizontal collectivism, whereas a military पदानुक्रम would be an उदाहरण of लंबवत collectivism.
Acute disseminated encephalomyelitis ( adem ) is an immune mediated बीमारी of the दिमाग.
it प्रायः occurs following a वाइरल संक्रमण लकिन may appear following vaccination, बैक्टीरियल or parasitic infection, or even appear अनायास.
As it involves autoimmune demyelination, it is समान to अनेक sclerosis, and is considered part of the अनेक काठिन्य borderline रोगों.
The incidence रेट is परिचय 8 प्रति 1,000,000 people per year.
हालांकि it occurs in सब ages, सबसे reported cases are in children and adolescents, साथ the average आयु around 5 to 8 years old.
the mortality रेट may be as high as 5 %, full recovery is देखी in 50 to 75 % of cases, while up to 70 to 90 % रिकवर साथ some minor residual विकलांगता.
The औसत time to रिकवर is एक to six months.
adem produces multiple inflammatory lesions in the दिमाग और spinal cord, विशेषकर in the white पदार्थ.
प्रायः these हैं मिला in the subcortical और central white matter और cortical gray-white junction of both दिमागी hemispheres, cerebellum, brainstem, और spinal cord, लकिन periventricular श्वेत पदार्थ and धूसर पदार्थ of the cortex, thalami and basal ganglia may भी be शामिल.
जब the रोगी suffers अधिक than one demyelinating episode, it is called तूल disseminated encephalomyelitis or multiphasic disseminated encephalomyelitis ( mdem ).
the पेट is a muscular, खोखला, dilated भाग of the digestion system which functions as an महत्वपूर्ण organ of the digestive ट्रैक्ट in कुछ animals, including vertebrates, echinoderms, कीट ( mid-gut ), and molluscs.
it is involved in the second phase of पाचन, following mastication ( चबाने ).
the stomach is स्तिथ between the ग्रासनाल और the छोटी intestine.
It secretes protein-digesting enzymes पुकारा protease और दमदार acids to सहायता in खाना पाचन, ( sent to it via esophageal peristalsis ) through चिकना muscular contortions ( पुकारा segmentation ) before sending partially digested खाना ( chyme ) to the small आंतों.
the word stomach is derived इससे the लैटिन stomachus जिससे is derived from the Greek शब्द stomachos ( στόμαχος ), ultimately from stoma ( ), `` मुँह ''.
the शब्द gastro- और gastric ( अर्थ सम्बन्धित to the पेट ) हैं both derived इससे the यूनानी word gaster ( ).

A woodie is a car देह style, विशेषकर a स्टेशन वैगन, जहाँ the पश्च bodywork is constructed of लकडी framework साथ infill panels of wood or चित्रित मेटल.

in 2008, wood construction was evoked abstractly on the घाट फ्लेक्स साथ a series of पक्ष और पश्च आड़ा डोले.
a पर्ल is a hard object उत्पादित within the soft ऊतक ( specifically the mantle ) of a जीना shelled mollusc.
बस जैसे the shell of a clam, a पर्ल is बना up of कैल्सियम कार्बोनेट in मिनट crystalline रूप, जिससे has महरूम deposited in concentric परतों.
the ideal पर्ल is perfectly round और smooth, but many अन्य आकार of pearls ( baroque मोती ) occur.
The finest quality प्राकृतिक pearls have महरूम अत्यधिक valued as रत्नों and वस्तुएँ of beauty लिये अनेक सदियां, और because of इस, the word पर्ल has become a रूपक लिये कुछ बहुत विरल, fine, admirable, और मूल्यवान.
the सबसे valuable मोती occur अनायास in the जंगली, लकिन वे हैं अत्यधिक विरल.
These जंगली मोती are referred to as natural pearls.
Cultured or farmed pearls इससे pearl oysters and freshwater mussels मेक up the majority of those कि हैं फिलहाल बेची.
Imitation pearls are also widely बेची in inexpensive आभूषण, but the quality of their iridescence is प्रायः बहुत ग़रीब, और प्रायः, कृत्रिम pearls हैं easily विशिष्ट from वास्तविक मोती.
मोती have महरूम harvested और cultivated primarily लिये use in आभूषण, लकिन in the पास्ट वे यहूद also सिले onto lavish clothing.
मोती have भी been crushed और used in cosmetics, दवाइयाँ, और in पेंट formulations.
whether wild or cultured, gem quality मोती are लगभग सदा nacreous और, as is the interior of the शेल कि produces उन्हें.
however, almost सब species of shelled molluscs are सक्षम of producing मोती ( formally referred to as `` calcareous concretions '' by कुछ स्त्रोत ) of lesser shine or कम spherical shape.
हालांकि these may भी be legitimately referred to as `` pearls '' by gemological लैब्स and भी under u.S. संघीय Trade Commission नियम, and हैं formed in the वही रास्ता, सबसे of उन्हें have no value, except as curiosities.
Bing ( ज्ञात previously as सजीव ढूंढें, खिड़कियाँ सजीव Search, and MSN ढूंढें ) is a web search इंजन ( advertised as a `` निर्णय engine `` ) from microsoft.
bing थी unveiled by microsoft CEO स्टीव बाल्मर on may 28, 2009 at the सब बाते Digital सम्मेलन in सैन Diego for रिलीज on जून 1.
Notable changes शामिल the लिस्टिंग of search सुझाव while प्रश्नों हैं डाला and a सूची of सम्बन्धित searches ( पुकारा `` explore फलक '' ) based on semantic technology इससे Powerset which Microsoft purchased in 2008.
on July 29, 2009, microsoft और याहू ! घोषित a deal in which bing होता power याहू ! Search.
सब Yahoo ! Search global ग्राहक और partners are अपेक्षित to have बना the transition by जल्दी 2012.
In अक्तूबर 2011, bing घोषित it थी working on new back-end ढूंढें अवसंरचना, साथ the लक्ष्य of delivering तेज़ and थोड़ा अधिक प्रासंगिक ढूंढें परिणाम लिये उपयोक्ता.
ज्ञात as `` Tiger '', the new index-serving प्रौद्योगिकी रै been incorporated into Bing globally, since August 2011.

In American football, प्रत्येक team has ग्यारह players on the field at एक समय.

This has resulted in the विकास of तीन `` platoons '' of खिलाड़ी, the ठोकर ( the टोली with the बॉल, जो is trying to score ), the रक्षा ( the टोली trying to prevent the अन्य टोली from scoring, and to take the ball इससे them ), and the खास टीमों ( जो play in kicking situations ).
भीतर those platoons, विभिन्न विशिष्ट positions मौजूद depending on कया the player 's प्रमुख जॉब is.
the Irish लोगों ( or na hÉireannaigh ; ulster-scots : airish fowk ) हैं an ethnic समूह जो originate in आयरलैंड, an द्वीप in northwestern यूरोपीय.
Ireland has महरूम populated लिये around 9,000 सालो ( according to पुरातत्व अध्ययन, see प्रागैतिहासिक आयरलैंड ).
the Irish people 's earliest पूर्वजो हैं recorded in महापुरूष – वे हैं claimed to be descended इससे समूह ऐसे as the nemedians, Fomorians, fir Bolg, tuatha Dé Danann और the milesians.

The प्रमुख समूह that interacted साथ the आयरिश in the मध्य Ages शामिल the picts, Scots, और the Vikings.

There have been many notable Irish लोगों throughout इतिहास.
The 6th सदी Irish भिक्षु और missionary columbanus is regarded as एक of the `` fathers of Europe '', followed by kilian of Würzburg and vergilius of साल्जबर्ग.
The वैज्ञानिक रॉबर्ट बॉयल is considered the `` father of chemistry ``.
Famous Irish explorers शामिल Brendan the नाविक, रॉबर्ट mcclure, अर्नेस्ट Shackleton and Tom crean.

historically, करणों रै महरूम caused by राजनीती, अकाल and आर्थिक मुद्दे.
An अनुमानित 50 to 80 लाख people हैं वंशजों of आयरिश लोगों, primarily in the United Kingdom, the संयुक्त States, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, कनाडा और आइसलैंड ; वहीँ हैं also smaller numbers in Argentina, चिली, मैक्सिको, जमैका, बारबाडोस, दक्षिण Africa, नई जीलैंड, फ़्रांस, जर्मनी and Brazil.

the Hubble Space दूरदर्शी ( hst ) is a स्पेस telescope कि was carried into orbit by a स्पेस शटल in 1990 और remains in आपरेशन.
a एपर्चर telescope in कम धरती कक्षा, हबल 's four main यंत्र observe in the near ultraviolet, visible, और निकट इन्फ्रारेड.
the telescope is नामित बाद the astronomer एडविन हबल.
हबल 's कक्षा बाहर the distortion of धरती 's माहौल allows it to लो अत्यधिक शार्प बिंब with लगभग no पृष्ठभूमि लाइट.
हबल 's गहन फ़ील्ड have महरूम कुछ of the सबसे विस्तृत visible-light बिंब कभी, allowing a deep view into स्पेस और समय.
अनेक हबल observations have led to सफलताएँ in astrophysics, ऐसे as accurately determining the rate of expansion of the ब्रह्मांड.
Although नहीं the first space दूरदर्शी, हबल is one of the largest और सबसे versatile, और is well known as both a vital research औजार and a पब्लिक संबंध बून लिये खगोलशास्त्र.
the hst was निर्मित by the संयुक्त राज्य space एजेंसी नासा, साथ contributions इससे the European Space एजेंसी, और is संचालित by the स्पेस दूरदर्शी विज्ञान संस्थान.
the HST is one of NASA 's Great Observatories, साथ साथ the Compton Gamma रे वेधशाला, the Chandra x-ray वेधशाला, और the Spitzer Space Telescope.
Space telescopes यहूद प्रस्तावित as early as 1923.
हबल थी funded in the 1970s, साथ a proposed लॉन्च in 1983, but the project was घिरा by technical देरी, budget problems, और the चैलेंजर disaster.
जब finally launched in 1990, वैज्ञानिकों found that the प्रमुख दर्पण had महरूम मैदान incorrectly, compromising the telescope 's सामर्थ्य.
the दूरदर्शी थी लौटी to its intended quality by a servicing मिशन in 1993.
Hubble is the तभी telescope designed to be serviced in स्पेस by astronauts.
between 1993 और 2002, चार मिशन repaired, upgraded, और replaced प्रणालियों on the दूरदर्शी ; a पांचवां मिशन was रद्द on सुरक्षा grounds following the Columbia disaster.
however, बाद spirited पब्लिक चर्चा, नासा administrator माइक Griffin स्वीकृत एक फाइनल सर्विसिंग mission, समाप्त in 2009 by Space शटल Atlantis.
the दूरदर्शी is अभी expected to function until at तनिक 2013.
Its वैज्ञानिक successor, the James Webb स्पेस दूरदर्शी ( jwst ), is to be launched in 2018 or संभवतः later.
Anti-inflammatory refers to the property of a पदार्थ or treatment कि reduces सूजन.
anti-inflammatory दवाएँ मेक up परिचय half of analgesics, remedying pain by reducing सूजन as opposed to opioids, जिससे affect the सेंट्रल nervous प्रणाली.
the tonight दिखाएँ is a US late-night बात show that रै aired on NBC since 1954.
