ss एंड्रिया डोरिया.
Pronounced थी an समंदर liner लिये the Italian Line ( Società di navigazione Italia ) home ported in Genoa, इटली, most प्रसिद्ध लिये its डूब in 1956, when 52 people died ( 51 इससे immediate प्रभाव ).
Named बाद the 16th-century Genoese admiral Andrea Doria, the जलयान had a gross पंजीकरण tonnage of 29,100 और a क्षमता of परिचय 1,200 passengers and 500 क्रू.
For a country attempting to rebuild इसके economy और प्रतिष्ठा after संसार War II, Andrea डोरिया was an icon of इतालवी नेशनल pride.
of all Italy 's ships at the time, एंड्रिया डोरिया was the largest, fastest और supposedly safest.
शुभारम्भ on 16 June 1951, the ship undertook its maiden voyage on 14 जनवरी 1953.
on 25 July 1956, while the Andrea डोरिया थी approaching the coast of nantucket, Massachusetts, बंधी लिये नई यॉर्क City, the eastbound of the स्वीडिश American लकीर collided साथ it in कया became एक of history 's सबसे infamous maritime आपदाओं.
struck in the पक्ष, the top-heavy Andrea डोरिया तत्काल started to list severely to स्टारबोर्ड, which left हाफ of इसके lifeboats unusable.
the consequent shortage of lifeboats might have resulted in significant loss of जीवन, लकिन the दक्षता of the जलयान 's technical design अनुमत it to रहो afloat लिये over 11 hours after the ramming.
The शुभ बर्ताव of the crew, improvements in संचार और the रैपिड response of अन्य जहाजों averted a विपत्ति similar in स्केल to that of the in 1912.
1,660 यात्री and crew यहूद rescued और survived, while 46 लोगों died as a consequence of the collision.
the evacuated luxury लाइनर capsized और sank the following morning.
इस accident remains the worst maritime disaster to occur in संयुक्त राज्य waters since the sinking of the in 1915.
The घटना और its aftermath यहूद heavily covered by the न्यूज मीडिया.
While the बचाव प्रयत्न were दोनो successful और commendable, the cause of the टक्कर with the Stockholm और the loss of एंड्रिया Doria उत्पन्न much ब्याज in the मीडिया and अनेक lawsuits.
largely क्युकी of an out-of-court settlement अनुबंध between the two shipping कंपनियाँ during hearings immediately after the disaster, no determination of the कारण ( s ) was कभी formally प्रकाशित.
हालांकि वृहद दोष appeared initially to fall on the इतालवी लाइनर, more हाल discoveries have indicated कि a misreading of radar on the स्वीडिश जलयान may have initiated the टक्कर कोर्स, अग्रणी to त्रुटियाँ on both जहाजों.
Andrea Doria थी the last major transatlantic यात्री vessel to डूबना before aircraft became the पसन्दीदा विधि of सफर.
Dialysis tubing
डायलिसिस tubing is a type of semi- or partially permeable झिल्ली tubing बना from regenerated cellulose or सेलोफेन.
It can be प्रयुक्त for diffusion साथ solutes or परासरण if प्रयुक्त with जल तभी.
परासरण is when water गुजरता through a semi-permeable परत to पहुँचें संतुलन.
Diffusion, on the अन्य हाथ, allows the movement of अणुओं from ऊँची concentration to low concentration.
it होगा तभी allow molecules to pass through a semi-permeable झिल्ली or परत if the अणु is छोटी पर्याप्त to अनुरूप through the झिल्ली or a झिल्ली 's pore.
इस प्रायः परिणाम साथ the प्रभाव of diffusion through a झिल्ली तभी वाकई affects small molecules, and लगभग never larger अणुओं.
Dialysis tubing is प्रयुक्त in clinical circumstances to ensure a filtered प्रवाह of अणुओं, preventing the flow of larger solute अणुओं.
Small अणुओं can be `` धोया '' out of a समाधान which is उत्तेजित through the tubing into a solvent, usually जल, जिससे surrounds it और in जिससे वे can be flushed away.
In demonstrations of semi-permeable झिल्लियों, a solution containing several types of molecules, प्रायः ग्लूकोज और मंड, is लगाई into a semi-permeable डायलिसिस bag, such as a cellulose membrane साथ pores, और the थैला is sealed साथ a गांठ or elastic band.
The sealed dialysis bag is लगाई in a container of a different समाधान, or water.
अणुओं छोटी enough to pass through the tubing ( water, लवण, monosaccharides, और other small molecules ) tend to move into or आउट of the डायलिसिस थैला in the दिशा of अवरोहण concentration, इसलिए displaying diffusion.
larger अणुओं ( ऐसे as प्रोटीन, or polysaccharides ) that have dimensions significantly greater than the pore diameter are retained inside the डायलिसिस थैला.
the water और smaller solutes in a hypotonic समाधान ( a समाधान कि has a lesser solute concentration than the समाधान it is संदर्भित to ) होगा क्रॉस a semi-permeable membrane, जैसे डायलिसिस tubing, into a hypertonic समाधान ( a solution कि रै a उच्चतर solute विशेषज्ञता than the समाधान it is संदर्भित to ) in an attempt to reach संतुलन, जहाँ the solute विशेषज्ञता of प्रत्येक solution is in संतुलन.
Mercury प्रयोगशाला थर्मामीटर
A thermometer ( इससे the यूनानी, thermos, अर्थ `` hot '' और μἐτρον, metron, `` measure '' ) is a device कि उपायों temperature or तापमान gradient using a variety of अलग सिद्धान्त.
A थर्मामीटर रै दो महत्वपूर्ण तत्व : the temperature sensor ( e.g. the bulb on a mercury-in-glass थर्मामीटर ) in जिससे some physical बदलें occurs with तापमान, प्लस some अर्थात् of converting इस physical change into a numerical मान ( e.g. the दृश्य स्केल that is चिह्नित on a mercury-in-glass थर्मामीटर ).
वहीँ are अनेक types और अनेक uses लिये thermometers, as विस्तृत नीचे in भाग of इस आलेख.
हिम श्वेत और the Seven dwarfs is a 1937 अमरीकी एनिमेटेड musical fantasy film produced by वॉल्ट डिज़्नी और released by rko रेडियो Pictures.
Based on the जर्मनी fairy tale by the Brothers Grimm, it is the पहला full-length cel एनिमेटेड विशेषता फिल्मी और the earliest in the वॉल्ट डिज़्नी एनिमेटेड क्लासिक श्रेणी.
the स्टोरी थी adapted by storyboard artists डोरोथी Ann Blank, Richard Creedon, Merrill de मारिस, Otto englander, अर्ल Hurd, लंड Rickard, Ted सियर्स और Webb स्मिथ.

हिम श्वेत premiered at the carthay Circle थिएटर on दिसम्बर 21, 1937, followed by a देशभर release on फ़रवरी 4, 1938, और साथ अंतरराष्ट्रीय आय of $ 8 million दौरान its आरंभिक release briefly assumed the record of highest grossing ध्वनि film at the time.
the popularity of the film रै led to it होने re-released theatrically many टाइम्स, जबतक इसके घर वीडियो release in the 1990s.
Adjusted लिये महंगाई, it is one of the शीर्ष टेन performers at the उत्तर अमरीकी box दफ्तर.
At the 11th अकादमी Awards, वॉल्ट Disney थी awarded an मानद ऑस्कर, and the फिल्मी was nominated लिये बेहतरीन musical स्कोर.
It थी added to the संयुक्त राज्य नेशनल फिल्मी Registry in 1989 और is क्रमित in the अमरीकी Film Institute 's list of the 100 महानतम अमरीकी films, जो also named the film as the greatest अमरीकी animated फिल्मी of सब समय in 2008.
डिज़्नी 's लो on the fairy टेल रै था a बिग cultural impact, resulting in a लोकप्रिय थीम पार्क आकर्षण, a वीडियो game, and a ब्रॉडवे musical.
प्रसव, श्रमिक, delivery, जनम, partus, or parturition is the culmination of a गर्भावस्था period साथ the expulsion of एक or more नवजात infants from a woman 's uterus.
the process of सामान्य प्रसव is categorized in तीन चरण of श्रमिक : the shortening and dilation of the ग्रीवा, descent और जनम of the infant, and जनम of the placenta.
in many मामले and साथ increasing आवृत्ति, प्रसव is हासिल through induction of मजदूर or caesarean section, which is the removal of the neonate through a surgical incision in the abdomen, rather than through vaginal जनम.
Childbirth by c-sections increased 50 % in the u.S. from 1996 to 2006, और comprise nearly 32 % of births in the u.S. और कनाडा.
साथ आदर to induced labor, अधिक than 22 % of महिलाओं undergo प्रेरण of श्रमिक in the संयुक्त States.
Medical पेशेवर नीति makers ढूँढें कि induced births and elective cesarean can be नुकसानदेह to the fetus and neonate as खूब as नुकसानदेह or without लाभ to the mother, and have established सख्त guidelines लिये non-medically indicated induced births and elective cesarean before 39 weeks.

a पत्ता is an अंग of a vascular plant, as पारिभाषित in वनस्पति शर्तें, and in particular in संयंत्र morphology.
foliage is a mass संज्ञा that refers to पत्ते as a विशेषता of पौधे.
typically a पत्ता is a thin, flattened organ borne ऊपर मैदान and specialized लिये photosynthesis, but many प्रकार of leaves हैं adapted in तरीके almost unrecognisable in those शर्तें : some are not flat ( for उदाहरण अनेक succulent पत्ते और conifers ), कुछ हैं नहीं above मैदान ( ऐसे as बल्ब तराजू ), और कुछ are बगैर प्रमुख photosynthetic फलन ( consider लिये उदाहरण cataphylls, spines, और cotyledons ).
Conversely, अनेक structures of non-vascular पौधे, or भी of some lichens, जिससे are नहीं पौधे at all ( in the sense of होने members of the kingdom plantae ), do dekh and फलन much जैसे पत्ते.
furthermore, अनेक structures found in vascular पौधे dekh जैसे leaves but हैं नहीं actually leaves ; वे differ इससे leaves in their structures और origins.
उदाहरण include phyllodes, cladodes, और phylloclades.

हमारी Gang ( also known as The छोटी दुष्टों or Hal Roach 's दुष्टों ) हैं a श्रेणी of American कॉमेडी short films about a समूह of poor पड़ोस children और their adventures.
Created by comedy निर्माता एचएएल रोच, the series is noted for showing children behaving in a अपेक्षाकृत प्राकृतिक way, as रोच और असली director Robert F. mcgowan worked to फिल्मी the unaffected, कच्चा nuances apparent in regular children rather than have them imitate वयस्क acting styles.
in जोड, Our गिरोह notably put लड़कों, लड़कियों, whites and अश्वेतों साथ in a group as equals, कुछ कि `` broke नई ground, '' according to film इतिहासकार लियोनार्ड Maltin.
Such a thing had never महरूम किया पहले in सिनेमा लकिन रै चूंकि been repeated बाद the success of Our Gang.
The पहला production at the रोच स्टुडियो in 1922 was a श्रेणी of मूक छोटी subjects.
जब रोच बदला वितरकों from Pathé to metro-goldwyn-mayer ( mgm ) in 1927, और converted the श्रेणी to ध्वनि in 1929, the श्रेणी took बंद भी further.

The Our गिरोह श्रेणी शामिल a total of 220 शॉर्ट्स और एक विशेषता फिल्मी, सामान्य spanky, featuring over forty-one चाइल्ड अभिनेताओं.
as mgm retained the अधिकारों to the Our गिरोह trademark following उनके purchase of the उत्पादन अधिकारों, the 80 roach-produced `` टॉकीज़ '' were syndicated for टेलीविज़न अंतर्गत the शीर्षक The Little Rascals beginning in 1955.

झील Tahoe ( ; washo : dáʔaw ) is a large freshwater lake in the Sierra Nevada of the संयुक्त राज्य.
at a सतह उन्नयन of, it is स्तिथ along the किनारा between कैलिफ़ोर्निया और नेवाडा, west of कार्सन नगर.
Lake tahoe is the largest अल्पाइन lake in North America.
Its गहराई is, making it the United राज्य 's second-deepest ( the deepest is Crater Lake in ऑरेगॉन, being deeper, at ).

The झील was formed about 2 लाख years पहले and is a part of the Lake Tahoe जलाशय साथ the modern lake being shaped दौरान the ice आयु.
It is ज्ञात लिये the स्पष्टता of its water and the परिदृश्य of surrounding mountains on all पहलू.
the क्षेत्रफल surrounding the झील is भी referred to as झील tahoe, or simply tahoe.
झील Tahoe is a प्रमुख tourist आकर्षण in दोनो नेवाडा और California.

Snow और skiing हैं a significant part of the क्षेत्रफल 's अर्थव्यवस्था and reputation.

“first वे आए... ” is a famous बयान and उत्तेजक poem attributed to पादरी मार्टिन niemöller ( 1892–1984 ) परिचय the sloth of German intellectuals following the nazis ' rise to power और the subsequent purging of their चुनी लक्ष्य, समूह बाद समूह.

The Four तिहाई system is a मानक निर्मित by ओलम्पस and Kodak for डिजिटल single-lens reflex कैमरा ( dslr ) design और development. < ref name='dpreview.com 2001-02-13 ' >
The system provides a मानक that, साथ डिजिटल कैमरे and lenses उपलब्धियाँ from अनेक निर्माताओं, allows लिये the इंटरचेंज of lenses और bodies इससे different निर्माताओं.
seems to cover the मानक.
Proponents describe it as an खोलें मानक, but कंपनियाँ may only use it under a non-disclosure अनुबंध.
नापसंद पुरानी SLR प्रणालियों, Four तिहाई रै been designed from the मैदान up to be entirely digital.
Many lenses हैं extensively computerized, to the पाइंट that Olympus offers फर्मवेयर updates for many of उन्हें.
लेंस डिज़ाइन रै महरूम tailored to the आवश्यकताएँ of digital सेंसर, सबसे notably through telecentric डिजाइन.
the size of the सेंसर is significantly smaller than for सबसे DSLRs और इस implies that lenses, especially telephoto lenses, can be छोटी.
लिये उदाहरण, a Four तिहाई lens साथ a 300 mm फोकल लंबाई होता कवर परिचय the वही angle of view as a 600 mm focal लंबाई lens लिये the 35 mm फिल्मी standard, और is correspondingly more कॉम्पैक्ट.
Thus, the चार Thirds प्रणाली रै क्रॉप फ़ैक्टर ( फोकल लंबाई गुणक ) of about 2, and while this enables longer focal length लिये greater magnification, it करता n't aid the manufacture of चौड़ी angle lenses.
the image sensor स्वरूप, generally इंटरमीडिएट between those of larger slrs and छोटी compact cameras, generally gives levels of cost, प्रदर्शन and convenience इंटरमीडिएट between those two वर्ग.
hvac प्रणालियों उपयोग वेंटिलेशन air ducts installed throughout a building to supply conditioned air to a room through outlet vents, पुकारा diffusers ; and नलिकाएं to हटाएँ एयर through return-air grilles.
hvac ( हीटिंग, वेंटिलेशन, और एयर conditioning ) is the प्रौद्योगिकी of अंदर and ऑटोमोटिव environmental सुकून.
HVAC system design is a subdiscipline of mechanical engineering, आधारित on the सिद्धान्त of thermodynamics, fluid mechanics, और ऊष्मा transfer.
प्रशीतन is sometimes added to the field 's abbreviation as HVAC & R or HVACR, or ventilating is dropped as in hacr ( ऐसे as the नामांकन of hacr-rated circuit ब्रेकर्स ).
hvac is important in the डिज़ाइन of medium to large औद्योगिक और दफ्तर इमारतें such as skyscrapers and in समुद्री environments ऐसे as aquariums, जहाँ safe और healthy building शर्तें हैं regulated with आदर to temperature and आर्द्रता, using fresh एयर इससे बाहरी.
वेंटिलेशन on the downdraught प्रणाली, by impulsion, or the 'plenum ' principle, लागू to schoolrooms ( 1899 )
Heating, ventilating, and एयर कंडीशनिंग is आधारित on आविष्कारों और discoveries बना by निकोलय lvov, माइकल फैराडे, Willis वाहक, reuben trane, जेम्स Joule, William Rankine, sadi carnot, और अनेक अन्य.
the invention of the components of hvac प्रणालियों गई hand-in-hand with the औद्योगिक revolution, और new विधि of modernization, उच्चतर efficiency, and प्रणाली कंट्रोल हैं constantly introduced by कंपनियाँ और आविष्कारक worldwide.
The तीन सेंट्रल कृत्यों of heating, ventilating, और air-conditioning हैं interrelated, especially साथ the need to provide थर्मल सुकून and स्वीकार्य indoor एयर quality भीतर reasonable installation, आपरेशन, and मेंटेनेंस लागत.
HVAC systems can provide वेंटिलेशन, reduce air घुसपैठ, और maintain pressure संबंध between spaces.
the means of एयर delivery and हटाना इससे स्पेसेस is ज्ञात as रूम एयर distribution.
the starting पाइंट in carrying आउट an estimate दोनो लिये कूलिंग and heating depends on the exterior जलवायु और interior specified conditions.
however before लेने up the ऊष्मा लोड calculation, it is जरुरी to ढूँढें भैस air requirements लिये प्रत्येक क्षेत्रफल in विवरण, as pressurization is an महत्वपूर्ण consideration.
In modern buildings the डिज़ाइन, installation, और कंट्रोल प्रणालियों of these functions are integrated into एक or अधिक HVAC प्रणालियों.
For बहुत छोटी buildings, ठेकेदारों सामान्यतः क्षमता इंजीनियर and select HVAC प्रणालियों और उपकरण.
लिये larger इमारतें, building सेवाएं designers and इंजीनियर्स, ऐसे as mechanical, architectural, or building सेवाएं engineers analyze, डिज़ाइन, and बताएँ the HVAC systems, और specialty mechanical contractors fabricate और आयोग उन्हें.
भवन permits और code-compliance inspections of the संस्थापना हैं normally जरूरी लिये सब आकार of buildings.
the HVAC industry is a worldwide enterprise, with भूमिकाएँ सहित आपरेशन और maintenance, system design and construction, equipment manufacturing and बिक्री, और in शिक्षा और शोध.
the HVAC उद्योग was historically regulated by the निर्माताओं of hvac equipment, लकिन regulating और मानकों संगठन such as hardi, ASHRAE, smacna, ACCA, Uniform Mechanical कोड, International mechanical कोड, और amca have महरूम established to support the industry और encourage ऊँची मानकों और achievement.

louisiana ( or ;, ; louisiana Creole : léta de la lwizyàn ) is a राज्य located in the दक्षिणी region of the United राज्य of अमेरिका.
louisiana is the 31st सबसे extensive और the 25th सबसे populous of the 50 United States.
इसके capital is baton रूज and largest city is नई Orleans.
louisiana is the तभी राज्य in the U.S. साथ political subdivisions termed parishes, जिससे are लोकल सरकारी 's equivalent to counties.
the largest मोहल्ला by जनसांख्यिकी is East baton रूज मोहल्ला, and the largest by land क्षेत्रफल is Cameron Parish.
much of the राज्य 's lands यहूद formed from sediment धोया down the Mississippi नदी, leaving enormous deltas और विशाल क्षेत्रों of coastal दलदल और मग्न.
ये contain a rich दक्षिणी biota ; ठेठ examples शामिल पक्षियों such as आइबिस and egrets.
वहीँ are भी many प्रजाति of tree frogs, and fish ऐसे as sturgeon and paddlefish.
in more elevated क्षेत्रों, आग is a प्राकृतिक process in the landscape, और has produced extensive क्षेत्रों of longleaf पाइन वन और गीला savannas.
ये support an exceptionally विशाल number of संयंत्र प्रजाति, सहित many प्रजाति of orchids और मांसाहारी plants.
कुछ louisiana शहरी environments have a multicultural, बहुभाषी विरासत, होने so strongly बहकावे by an जिसमें of 18th-century फ्रेंच, स्पेनी, देशी अमरीकी ( Indian ) और African संस्कृतियों that वे are माना to be somewhat exceptional in the u.s.
पहले the अमरीकी purchase of the territory, the वर्तमान Louisiana State था महरूम both a स्पेनी and French उपनिवेश.
in जोड, the pattern of development included importing numerous African स्लेव in the 18th सदी, with अनेक from the वही प्रदेश of वेस्ट Africa, यूँ concentrating their culture.
In the post-Civil युद्ध environment, Anglo-Americans increased the pressure लिये Anglicization, और in 1915, अंग्रेज़ी थी बना the तभी आधिकारिक language of the state.
Women 's rights हैं the अधिकारों and entitlements claimed लिये women और लड़कियों of many societies विश्वव्यापी.
In कुछ places ये अधिकारों are institutionalized or समर्थित by विधि, लोकल कस्टम, और आचरण, whereas in अन्य they may be उपेक्षित or suppressed.
They differ इससे broader धारणाएं of इंसान rights through claims of an अंतर्निहित ऐतिहासिक and परंपरागत पूर्वाग्रह विरूद्ध the कसरत of rights by women और लड़कियों in favour of मेन and लड़कों.
मुद्दे commonly संबद्ध साथ धारणाएं of महिलाओं 's rights शामिल, हालांकि are नहीं सीमित to, the right : to bodily अखंडता और autonomy ; to vote ( suffrage ) ; to थाम पब्लिक दफ्तर ; to work ; to fair मजदूरी or equal pay ; to own प्रॉपर्टी ; to शिक्षा ; to serve in the military or be conscripted ; to डालें into legal अनुबंध ; and to have marital, parental and धार्मिक अधिकारों.
The कानून of विज्ञान or वैज्ञानिक कानून हैं कथन that describe, predict, और शायद explain क्यों, a दायरा of phenomena behave as they appear to in प्रकृति.
the पद `` विधि '' has विविध उपयोग in अनेक cases : approximate, सटीक, व्यापक or narrow theories, in सब प्राकृतिक scientific disciplines ( भौतिकी, chemistry, biology, भूविज्ञान, astronomy etc. ).
an analogous term लिये a scientific विधि is a principle.
Scientific विधिs:
summarize a large collection of facts संकल्पित by experiment into a single statement,
can प्रायः be प्रतिपादित mathematically as एक or अनेक कथन or समीकरण, or at तनिक stated in a single वाक्य, so that it can be प्रयुक्त to भविष्यवाणी the निष्कर्ष of an प्रयोग, दिए the initial, boundary, और other शारीरिक conditions of the प्रक्रियाओं जिससे take place,
are strongly समर्थित by empirical प्रमाण - वे हैं scientific ज्ञान that प्रयोग have repeatedly verified ( और never falsified ).
Their accuracy करता not बदलें जब नई theories हैं worked आउट, लकिन बल्कि the scope of अनुप्रयोग, चूंकि the समीकरण ( if कोई ) representing the law करता नहीं change.
as साथ अन्य वैज्ञानिक ज्ञान, वे do not have निरपेक्ष certainty like mathematical theorems or identities, और it is सदा संभावित for a विधि to be overturned by भविष्य observations.
are प्रायः quoted as a आधारभूत controlling influence बल्कि than a वर्णन of observed तथ्य.
I.e. `` the कानून of गति require कि ''
कानून differ इससे hypotheses and postulates, which are proposed दौरान the वैज्ञानिक प्रक्रम before और during validation by experiment and अवलोकन.
ये हैं not कानून चूंकि वे have नहीं महरूम verified to the same उपाधि और may नहीं be sufficiently general, हालांकि they may lead to the formulation of laws.
a law is a more solidified और formal statement, आसुत इससे repeated प्रयोग.
Although the अवधारणाओं of a law or principle in nature is borderline to दर्शनशास्त्र, and presents the depth to जिससे गणित can describe nature, वैज्ञानिक कानून हैं considered from a वैज्ञानिक perspective और follow the scientific method ; वे `` serve their purpose '' rather than `` questioning वास्तविकता '' ( philosophical ) or `` statements of लॉजिकल absolution '' ( गणितीय ).
For उदाहरण, whether a विधि `` refers to वास्तविकता '' is a philosophical समस्या, rather than वैज्ञानिक.
Fundamentally, सब वैज्ञानिक laws follow from physics, laws which occur in अन्य sciences ultimately follow इससे physical laws.
प्रायः, from mathematically आधारभूत viewpoints, universal constants emerge इससे scientific कानून.

ब्लैक pepper ( Piper nigrum ) is a flowering बेल in the परिवार Piperaceae, cultivated लिये its fruit, which is usually सूखी और used as a मसाला और seasoning.
The फल, ज्ञात as a peppercorn when dried, is लगभग in diameter, अंधेरा रेड जब fully वयस्क, और, जैसे all drupes, contains a सिंगल बीज.
Peppercorns, और the ground pepper निकला इससे उन्हें, may be वर्णित simply as pepper, or more precisely as ब्लैक pepper ( पकाया and सूखी unripe फल ), ग्रीन pepper ( सूखी unripe फल ) and white pepper ( dried ripe बीज ).
ब्लैक pepper is देशी to दक्षिण India, and is extensively cultivated वहीँ और elsewhere in तीव्र regions.
फिलहाल वियतनाम is the संसार 's largest निर्माता and exporter of pepper, producing 34 % of the world 's पाइपर nigrum क्रॉप as of 2008.
सूखी मैदान pepper has महरूम प्रयुक्त since प्राचीनता for both इसके फ्लेवर और as a आयुर्विज्ञान.
ब्लैक pepper is the संसार 's सबसे traded spice.
it is एक of the most आम मसाले added to European भोजन और इसके वंशजों.
the spiciness of black pepper is due to the chemical piperine, नहीं to be उलझन साथ the capsaicin कि देता मांसल peppers theirs.
it is in the आधुनिक संसार, often युग्म साथ salt.
in cardiovascular physiology, ejection fraction ( EF ) represents the आयतनी भिन्न of blood pumped आउट of the ventricle ( दिल ) with each दिल ताल or हृदय साईकिल.
it can be लागू to either the सही ventricle which ejects via the pulmonary वाल्व into the pulmonary circulation or the left ventricle which ejects via the aortic वाल्व into the प्रणालीगत परिसंचरण.
Imaging of the physiology of the mammalian दिल is the art कि allows सार्थक mathematical expression धमक ef.
noninvasive cardiac इमेजिंग has become a विश्वव्यापी utility enabling study of हृदय प्रदर्शन reproducibly and inexpensively.
Simplified, ejection fraction is a mathematical product अनुमत by cardiac इमेजिंग.
As a गणितीय पद, ejection भिन्न is an एक्सटेंशन of the work of एडाल्फ फिक in cardiac output.
समर्पित technology such as इकोकार्डियोग्राफी, computed टोमोग्राफी, चुम्बकीय अनुनाद इमेजिंग और MUGA स्कैनिंग have definitively अनुमत clinically प्रासंगिक गणित regarding ischemia, जन्मजात दिल बीमारी और Heart विफलता.
the अभियोजक is the मुख्य legal प्रतिनिधि of the अभियोजन in देशों with either the common विधि adversarial प्रणाली, or the सिविल law inquisitorial प्रणाली.
The prosecution is the legal party responsible लिये presenting the case in a दण्ड विचारण against an व्यक्तिगत अभियुक्त of breaking the विधि.

Abū al-qāsim Muḥammad इब्न ʿabd allāh इब्न ʿAbd al-muṭṭalib इब्न Hāshim ( ) ( circa| 570 – circa| 8 जून 632 ), also transliterated as मुहम्मद ( ), थी a religious, political, and सैन्य नेता from Mecca जो एकीकृत अरब into a सिंगल धार्मिक polity under islam.
he is believed by मुसलमान और Bahá'ís to be a मेसेंजर and prophet of God.
Muhammad is लगभग universally माना by मुसलमान as the पिछला prophet भेजा by परमेश्वर for mankind.
non-muslims लिहाज़ मुहम्मद as the संस्थापक of Islam.
मुसलमान consider उसे to be the restorer of an unaltered असली monotheistic आस्था of Adam, Noah, Abraham, मूसा, यीशु, and other नबियों.
Born in about 570 CE in the arabian नगर of मक्का, he थी orphaned at an early age और brought up अंतर्गत the परवाह of उसके ताऊ Abu तालिब.
he later worked mostly as a व्यापारी, as खूब as a shepherd, और थी पहला married by आयु 25.
होने in the आदत of periodically retreating to a cave in the surrounding mountains for अनेक नाइट्स of seclusion और दुआ, he later reported कि it थी there, at age 40, that he प्राप्त उसके first रहस्योद्घाटन from परमेश्वर.
Three years बाद इस इवेंट मुहम्मद प्रारंभ preaching ये खुलासे publicly, proclaiming कि `` परमेश्वर is One ``, that complete `` surrender '' to Him ( lit.
islām ) is the तभी रास्ता ( dīn ) स्वीकार्य to परमेश्वर, और कि he himself थी a नबी और मेसेंजर of God, in the वही रग as other इस्लामी prophets.
मुहम्मद gained few followers जल्दी on, and थी मिले साथ दुश्मनी इससे कुछ Meccan जनजातियों ; he and उसके अनुसरणकर्ता यहूद treated harshly.
To एस्केप persecution, Muhammad sent कुछ of his followers to Abyssinia पहले he और उसके अनुसरणकर्ता in Mecca migrated to मदीना ( तब known as Yathrib ) in the साल 622.
इस इवेंट, the हिज्र, marks the beginning of the इस्लामी पंचांग, जिससे is भी ज्ञात as the hijri Calendar.
In Medina, Muhammad united the जनजातियों under the संविधान of Medina.
बाद आठ years of लड़ साथ the meccan जनजातियों, his अनुसरणकर्ता, who by तब had grown to 10,000, took control of Mecca in the largely शांतिपूर्ण Conquest of Mecca.
he destroyed the pagan मूर्तियों in the नगर और तब भेजा his followers आउट to नष्ट सब of the remaining pagan मंदिरों in पूर्वी अरब.
in 632, a few months after returning to मदीना इससे The विदाई Pilgrimage, मुहम्मद fell ill और died.
by the time of उसके मौत, most of the arabian Peninsula था परिवर्तित to islam, और he था संयुक्त Arabia into a सिंगल Muslim religious polity.
the खुलासे ( or ayah, lit.
`` लक्षण [ of परमेश्वर ] '' ) — which मुहम्मद reported receiving until his मौत – रूप the verses of the Quran, regarded by मुसलमान as the `` शब्द of God '' और around जिससे the धर्म is based.
besides the कुरान, मुहम्मद 's life ( सिरा ) और परंपराओं ( सुन्नत ) हैं also upheld by Muslims as the स्त्रोत of शरीयत law.
वे discuss Muhammad and other prophets of islam साथ reverence, adding the phrase peace be upon उसे whenever their names are mentioned.
जबकि conceptions of मुहम्मद in medieval Christendom and premodern टाइम्स यहूद largely ऋणात्मक, appraisals in modern history have महरूम दूर less so.
the ग्रेट किताबे ( दूसरी संस्करण )
Great Books of the पश्चिमी संसार is a श्रेणी of किताबे originally प्रकाशित in the United राज्य in 1952 by ब्रिटैनिका विश्वकोष inc. to present the Great किताबे in a सिंगल पैकेज of 54 volumes.
The series is now in इसके दूसरी संस्करण and contains 60 आयतन.
the असली सम्पादक of the series chose तीन criteria for समावेश : a किताब must be प्रासंगिक to contemporary मुद्दे, and नहीं only important in its historical कॉन्टेक्स्ट ; it must reward rereading ; और it जरूर be a भाग of `` the great वार्तालाप परिचय the great ideas, '' relevant to at least 25 of the 102 ग्रेट ideas identified by the editors.
किताबे यहूद not चुनी on the basis of जातीय or सांस्कृतिक inclusiveness, ऐतिहासिक influence, or the editors ' agreement साथ the दृश्य expressed.

the आधार was attacked by 353 Japanese fighters, bombers and torpedo planes in दो लहरें, launched from छह वायुयान वाहक.

एक जापानी sailor was captured.

In numismatics, a खच्चर is a coin or पदक minted with obverse and reverse डिजाइन not सामान्यतः देखी on the same टुकड़ा.

This type of error is अत्यधिक sought बाद, और उदाहरण can लाने steep prices इससे collectors.

खिड़कियाँ powershell is Microsoft 's कार्य automation फ्रेमवर्क, consisting of a command-line शेल and associated scripting language निर्मित on.neT फ्रेमवर्क.
powershell provides पूरा access to COM और wmi, enabling administrators to perform प्रशासनिक कार्य on दोनो local and remote खिड़कियाँ प्रणालियों.
in powershell, प्रशासनिक कार्य हैं generally performed by cmdlets ( सुनाया command-lets ), which हैं specialized.NET वर्ग implementing a particular आपरेशन.
Sets of cmdlets may be combined together in scripts, executables ( जिससे हैं standalone अनुप्रयोग ), or by instantiating नियमित.neT classes ( or wmi/com Objects ).
ये work by accessing आंकड़ा in अलग data stores, like the filesystem or रजिस्ट्री, which are बना available to the PowerShell runtime via खिड़कियाँ powershell प्रदाताओं.
खिड़कियाँ powershell भी provides a hosting api with which the Windows PowerShell runtime can be embedded inside अन्य applications.
These अनुप्रयोग can then उपयोग Windows PowerShell functionality to implement निश्चित परिचालन, सहित those उजागर via the आलेखीय इंटरफ़ेस.
इस काबिलियत रै महरूम प्रयुक्त by Microsoft Exchange Server 2007 to expose इसके management functionality as powershell cmdlets और प्रदाताओं और implement the graphical प्रबन्धन टूल्स as powershell होस्ट which invoke the necessary cmdlets.
अन्य microsoft अनुप्रयोग including microsoft SQL Server 2008 also expose their management interface via powershell cmdlets.
साथ powershell, graphical interface-based management अनुप्रयोग on खिड़कियाँ हैं layered on top of खिड़कियाँ PowerShell.
A powershell एनक्रिप्शन interface for खिड़कियाँ उत्पाद is mandated by the Common अभियान्त्रिकी मापदण्ड.
खिड़कियाँ powershell शामिल इसके अपना extensive, console-based सहायता, समान to man pages in Unix shells, via the get-help cmdlet.

A स्टोरी चाप is an extended or continuing storyline in episodic storytelling मीडिया ऐसे as टेलीविज़न, comic books, कॉमिक strips, boardgames, video games, and in some मामले, films.
on a television program, for उदाहरण, the स्टोरी होता unfold over अनेक episodes.
in टेलीविज़न, the use of the स्टोरी चाप is much अधिक common in dramas than in comedies, विशेषकर in साबुन operas.
webcomics are more संभावित to उपयोग story arcs than समाचारपत्र comics, as सबसे web comics have पठनीय अभिलेख online कि a newcomer to the स्ट्रिप can read in अनुक्रम to समझे कया is going on.
Although स्टोरी arcs have existed for decades, the पद `` स्टोरी चाप '' थी coined in 1988 in संबंध to the टेलीविज़न series wiseguy, और थी जल्दी adapted लिये other उपयोग.
अनेक American कॉमिक किताब श्रेणी हैं now written in चार or six-issue arcs, भीतर a continuing series.
Short story arcs हैं easier to package as trade paperbacks for पुनर्विक्रय, और अधिक accessible to the कैज़ुअल reader than the never-ending निरंतरता कि once characterised कॉमिक्स.
Black शुक्रवार is the day following Thanksgiving Day in the United राज्य, often regarded as the शुरूआत of the Christmas खरीदारी ऋतु.
in हाल years, सबसे major रिटेलर have खोली अत्यधिक early और offered promotional बिक्री to लात off the holiday shopping season, similar to मुक्केबाज़ी दिन बिक्री in अनेक राष्ट्रमंडल Nations.
ब्लैक Friday is नहीं an official public अवकाश as such, but अनेक non-retail कर्मचारी and स्कूलों have दोनो थैंक्सगिविंग और the day after बंद, followed by a वीकेंड, thereby increasing the number of potential shoppers.
It रै routinely महरूम the busiest खरीदारी day of the साल चूंकि 2005, हालांकि news रिपोर्ट्स, जिससे at कि time यहूद inaccurate, have described it as the busiest shopping दिन of the साल लिये a much longer period of समय.
the day 's नाम originated in Philadelphia, जहाँ it originally was used to describe the भारी and disruptive pedestrian and vehicle ट्रैफ़िक जिससे would occur on the दिन after थैंक्सगिविंग.
Use of the term प्रारंभ before 1961 और began to see broader use outside फिलाडेल्फिया around 1975.
बाद an alternative explanation began to be offered : कि `` ब्लैक शुक्रवार '' indicates the पाइंट at जिससे रिटेलर begin to turn a profit, or are `` ''.
लिये अनेक सालो, it थी आम लिये रिटेलर to open at 6:00 a.m., लकिन in the late 2000s अनेक था crept to 5:00 or even 4:00.
This was taken to a नई चरम in 2011, when अनेक रिटेलर ( including निशाना, kohl 's, macy 's, बेहतरीन Buy, and bealls ) opened at मध्यरात्रि लिये the first time.
in 2012, walmart और several other retailers announced कि they होता खोलें most of उनके स्टोर्स at 8:00 p.m. on Thanksgiving Day ( except in राज्य where खोलने on Thanksgiving is prohibited due to ब्लू कानून, such as Massachusetts जहाँ वे स्टिल खोली around मध्यरात्रि ), prompting काल्स लिये a walkout among कुछ workers.
ब्लैक शुक्रवार shopping is ज्ञात लिये attracting आक्रामक crowds, साथ सालाना reports of assaults, shootings, and throngs of लोगों trampling on अन्य shoppers in an attempt to मिलेंगी the बेहतरीन सौदे on a उत्पाद पहले आपूर्तियाँ run out.

the अंग्रेजों West इंडीज यहूद the आइलैंड्स in और around the caribbean that यहूद भाग of the British Empire.
In 1912, the अंग्रेजों West Indies यहूद विभाजित into आठ colonies : the Bahamas, Barbados, British Guiana, British Honduras, जमैका ( साथ इसके dependencies the Turks and caicos Islands और the केमन आइलैंड्स ), Trinidad and टोबैगो, the Windward Islands और the leeward Islands.
Between 1958 और 1962, सब of the द्वीप territories except the British वर्जिन आइलैंड्स, the बहामा, अंग्रेजों होंडुरास and अंग्रेजों guiana यहूद organised into the वेस्ट इंडीज संघ.
it was hoped कि the संघ would become independent as a single nation, but it had सीमित शक्तियां, अनेक व्यावहारिक problems, and a कमी of लोकप्रिय support.
नतीजतन, the वेस्ट इंडीज संघ was dissolved.
सबसे of the territories, सहित सब the larger ones, हैं अभी स्वतंत्र as पृथक देशों, with membership to अनेक अंतरराष्ट्रीय forums ऐसे as the संगठन of American राज्य, the संघ of caribbean राज्य, the संसार Trade Organization, the संयुक्त Nations, the caribbean Community, the राष्ट्रमंडल of राष्ट्र and the caribbean विकास बैंको among अन्य.
the शेष are अंग्रेजों overseas territories.
All the former राष्ट्र of the अंग्रेजों वेस्ट इंडीज, मगर the राष्ट्रमंडल of डोमिनिकन, Guyana and त्रिनिदाद और Tobago, हैं Commonwealth realms.

the inauguration of the अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य is a ceremonial इवेंट marking the शुरुआत of a नई four-year पद of a अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य.
The day a अध्यक्षीय उद्घाटन occurs is ज्ञात as `` Inauguration दिन '' और occurs on January 20 ( or 21st if the 20th is a संडे ).
( Prior to the Twentieth Amendment, the date थी कूच 4, the दिन of the साल on which the Constitution of the United राज्य first took प्रभाव in 1789 ; the last उद्घाटन to लो प्लेस on the पुरानी तिथि was Franklin D. Roosevelt 's पहला एक on March 4, 1933. )
The most recent पब्लिक presidential उद्घाटन रस्म, the swearing in of President बराक Obama to शुरू उसके दूसरी four-year term in दफ्तर, took प्लेस on सोमवार, जनवरी 21, 2013.
the only inauguration तत्व mandated by the United राज्य संविधान is कि the अध्यक्ष मेक an शपथ or प्रतिज्ञान पहले that person can `` डालें on the निष्पादन '' of the दफ्तर of the presidency.
However, over the सालो, various परंपराओं have arisen that have विस्तारित the उद्घाटन from a सरल oath-taking ceremony to a day-long event, सहित parades, भाषणों, और गेंदें.
इससे the प्रेसिडेंसी of एंड्रयू Jackson through that of Jimmy कार्टर, the primary उद्घाटन Day रस्म took place on the कैपिटल 's East portico.
Since the 1981 उद्घाटन of Ronald reagan, the रस्म has महरूम आयोजित at the Capitol 's वेस्ट Front.
The inaugurations of William हावर्ड Taft in 1909 और Reagan in 1985 were स्थानांतरित indoors at the कैपिटल due to ठंडा मौसम.
the युद्ध of 1812 and संसार War ii caused two inaugurations to be आयोजित at अन्य स्थितियाँ in वॉशिंगटन, D.C.
जब जार्ज वॉशिंगटन थी inaugurated, the oath थी administered by Robert livingston, Chancellor of New यॉर्क State, in 1789, और by विलियम Cushing, Associate इंसाफ of the Supreme अदालत, in 1793.
Since मुख्य Justice Oliver एल्सवर्थ swore in President जॉन एडम्स, no मुख्य justice रै छूटी an उद्घाटन दिन.
When Inauguration दिन रै गिरे on a Sunday, the मुख्य इंसाफ रै administered the oath to the president on the Sunday privately और तब again the अगला दिन publicly.
When a नई president takes over mid-term due to the मौत or इस्तीफा of a president, the शपथ of दफ्तर is administered लकिन formal, पब्लिक inauguration कार्यक्रम have not been held.

She जल्द began performing in the चट्टान म्यूज़िक झाँकी of Manhattan 's निम्नतर East Side.
By the समाप्त of 2007, record कार्यपालिका and निर्माता विंसेंट हर्बर्ट signed her to उसके label streamline Records, an imprint of interscope Records.

महिला गागा came to prominence as a रिकॉर्डिंग कलाकार following the रिलीज of उसके डेब्यू album, The Fame ( 2008 ), जिससे थी a critical and commercial कामयाबी that topped charts around the संसार और शामिल the international number-one singles `` Just नृत्य `` and `` Poker फेस ``.

As of October 2011, she रै sold an अनुमानित 23 million एल्बम और 64 लाख singles worldwide और her singles हैं some of the best-selling worldwide.

Lady गागा has consecutively appeared on बिलबोर्ड magazine 's कलाकारों of the साल ( स्कोरिंग the definitive title in 2010 ), ranked fourth in vh1 's list of 100 Greatest महिलाओं in Music, is the छठे best selling डिजिटल singles artist in US according to riaa, is regularly लगाई on सूचियाँ रचित by फोर्ब्स magazine and थी नामित one of the सबसे influential लोगों in the संसार by समय magazine.

a राजनैतिक campaign is an organized प्रयत्न which seeks to influence the निर्णय बनाना प्रक्रम भीतर a विशिष्ट group.
in democracies, राजनैतिक campaigns प्रायः refer to चुनावी campaigns, wherein प्रतिनिधि हैं chosen or referendums are decided.
In आधुनिक राजनीती, the most ऊँची प्रोफ़ाइल राजनैतिक अभियान हैं focused on candidates for head of राज्य or सिर of सरकारी, often a अध्यक्ष or प्रधान मंत्री.
एलिज़ाबेथ cady stanton and उसके बेटी, Harriot
Elizabeth Cady stanton ( November 12, 1815 – October 26, 1902 ) was an अमरीकी सोशल activist, abolitionist, और अग्रणी फिगर of the जल्दी women 's अधिकारों गति.
उसके घोषणा of sentiments, presented at the पहला महिलाओं 's अधिकारों convention आयोजित in 1848 in Seneca Falls, नई York, is often credited with initiating the पहला व्यवस्थित women 's rights and महिलाओं 's suffrage movements in the संयुक्त States.
Before stanton narrowed her political फ़ोकस almost exclusively to महिलाओं 's अधिकारों, वो थी an active abolitionist together with उसके husband, हेनरी Brewster stanton और cousin, gerrit Smith.
Unlike अनेक of those शामिल in the महिलाओं 's अधिकारों movement, stanton addressed various issues pertaining to women beyond मतदान अधिकारों.
Her concerns included women 's parental और कस्टडी अधिकारों, property rights, नियुक्ति and आय अधिकारों, तलाक, the economic स्वास्थ्य of the परिवार, और birth कंट्रोल.
She was भी an outspoken समर्थक of the 19th-century temperance गति.
बाद the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध, Stanton 's प्रतिबद्धता to मादा suffrage caused a schism in the महिलाओं 's अधिकारों गति when वो, साथ साथ सुसान B. एंथोनी, अस्वीकृत to support ड्योढ़ी of the fourteenth और पंद्रहवीं Amendments to the संयुक्त States Constitution.
वो opposed giving added legal सुरक्षा और मतदान अधिकारों to अफ़्रीकी अमरीकी मेन जबकि महिलाओं, ब्लैक और white, were अस्वीकृत those same अधिकारों.
उसके स्थिति on इस issue, साथ with her thoughts on organized christianity और महिलाओं 's मुद्दे परे मतदान अधिकारों, led to the गठन of दो separate महिलाओं 's अधिकारों संगठन that यहूद आखिरकार rejoined, साथ Stanton as president of the संयुक्त organization, approximately twenty सालो बाद उसके ब्रेक इससे the असली महिलाओं 's suffrage गति.
stanton died in 1902 having authored both The स्त्री 's बाइबल and उसके आत्मकथा, along with many articles and pamphlets concerning female suffrage and महिलाओं 's अधिकारों.

नस्ल or ethnic समूह is a socially defined category आधारित on आम culture or राष्ट्रीयता.

जातीय पहचान is constantly reinforced through common characteristics which नियत the समूह apart from other groups.
The 19.9 MW gemasolar solar संयंत्र in Spain features 15 hours of storage and can supply शक्ति 24 hours a day.
Solar उर्जा, रौशन light और heat from the sun, रै been harnessed by इंसानो चूंकि ancient टाइम्स using a दायरा of ever-evolving technologies.
Solar उर्जा technologies include solar हीटिंग, solar photovoltaics, solar थर्मल विद्युत, सौर वास्तुकला and artificial photosynthesis, जिससे can मेक considerable योगदान to solving some of the सबसे तात्कालिक उर्जा समस्याएं the world अभी चेहरों.
सौर technologies हैं broadly characterized as either passive सौर or active सौर depending on the रास्ता वे capture, बदलें और वितरित सौर energy.
क्रियाशील सौर तकनीकों शामिल the use of photovoltaic panels और solar thermal collectors to दोहन the energy.
Passive सौर तकनीकों शामिल orienting a भवन to the Sun, selecting सामग्री साथ favorable thermal द्रव्यमान or light dispersing गुण, और डिजाइनिंग spaces that naturally circulate एयर.
in 2011, the International उर्जा एजेंसी कहा कि `` the विकास of सस्ती, inexhaustible और साफ सौर energy technologies will have विशाल longer-term benefits.
it will बढ़ाएँ countries’ उर्जा सुरक्षा through reliance on an indigenous, inexhaustible and ज़्यादातर import-independent संसाधन, enhance स्थिरता, reduce प्रदूषण, निम्नतर the लागत of mitigating जलवायु बदलें, and रखना fossil ईंधन कीमतें निम्नतर than वरना.

The classical लैटिन वर्णमाला or Roman alphabet evolved इससे a western किस्में of the यूनानी वर्णमाला पुकारा the Cumaean वर्णमाला, जिससे थी अपनाया और परिवर्धित by the Etruscans who ruled जल्दी Rome.
the etruscan वर्णमाला थी in फेरे अपनाया और further परिवर्धित by the प्राचीन romans to लिखें the लैटिन भाषा.
During the मध्य Ages, the Latin वर्णमाला was adapted to रोमांस भाषाएं, सीधा descendants of लैटिन, as well as to Celtic, germanic, बाल्टिक, and some Slavic भाषाएं.
With the age of उपनिवेशवाद और ईसाई evangelism, the लैटिन स्क्रिप्ट थी spread overseas, और लागू to indigenous American, ऑस्ट्रेलियाई, Austronesian, austroasiatic, और अफ़्रीकी भाषाएं.
अधिक recently, linguists have भी tended to prefer the लैटिन स्क्रिप्ट or the अंतरराष्ट्रीय ध्वन्यात्मक वर्णमाला ( itself largely आधारित on लैटिन script ) जब transcribing or creating लिखा मानकों for non-european languages, such as the अफ़्रीकी reference वर्णमाला.
the term लैटिन वर्णमाला may refer to either the alphabet प्रयुक्त to write लैटिन ( as वर्णित in this article ), or other alphabets आधारित on the Latin स्क्रिप्ट, जिससे is the basic नियत of अक्षर common to the विभिन्न alphabets descended इससे the classical लैटिन एक, ऐसे as the English वर्णमाला.
ये latin-derived alphabets may discard letters, like the rotokas वर्णमाला, or add new letters, जैसे the डैनिश और Norwegian alphabet.
अक्षर shapes have बदला over the सदियां, including the creation लिये मध्यकालीन लैटिन of lower मामला फ़ॉर्म which किया not exist in the शास्त्रीय काल.
the assassination of संयुक्त राज्य President अब्राहम Lincoln took place on शुभ शुक्रवार, April 14, 1865, as the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध was drawing to a close.
the हत्या occurred पाँच दिनों after the कमांडर of the Confederate फौज of उत्तरी Virginia, सामान्य रॉबर्ट E. Lee, surrendered to लेफ्टिनेंट सामान्य Ulysses S. ग्रान्ट और the संघ फौज of the Potomac.
lincoln थी the पहला American president to be assassinated, हालांकि an unsuccessful attempt had महरूम made on एंड्रयू जैक्सन 30 सालो पहले in 1835.
the assassination थी नियोजित and carried out by the well-known stage actor जॉन wilkes बूथ, as भाग of a larger षड्यंत्र in a bid to revive the Confederate कारण.
बूथ 's co-conspirators यहूद लुईस Powell and दाउद Herold, who यहूद आबंटित to मार Secretary of राज्य विलियम H. seward, and जार्ज atzerodt who थी to मार Vice अध्यक्ष Andrew Johnson.
By simultaneously eliminating the शीर्ष three लोगों in the प्रशासन, Booth and his co-conspirators hoped to sever the continuity of the United राज्य government.
Lincoln थी शॉट जबकि watching the play Our American cousin साथ his wife मरियम टॉड lincoln at Ford 's Theatre in वॉशिंगटन, d.C. on the रात्रि of April 14, 1865.
He died early the अगला morning.
the बाकी of the conspirators ' plot विफल ; पावेल तभी managed to wound seward, जबकि atzerodt, जॉनसन 's would-be हत्यारे, खोया उसके nerve और fled वॉशिंगटन.

क्लबों level seating is a special section of seating in modern खेल stadiums.
the क्लबों Level is usually located towards the मध्य of the stage of seating sections, above the lower डेक but below the अपर deck.
They are प्रायः right अगला to the Luxury Boxes, either right ऊपर, सही नीचे, or sandwiched between दो levels of लक्ज़री Boxes.
Club स्तर seating is माना as higher क्लास than बैठे anywhere else in the एरिना, लकिन lower क्लास compared to the लक्ज़री बाक्स.
Unlike the लक्ज़री बाक्स, most क्लबों levels do नहीं रैप entirely around the एरिना.
Some क्लबों levels stop at a certain point, giving रास्ता to an expansion of the मेज़ानाइन, while others दे रास्ता to lower क्लास Luxury बाक्स ( ऐसे as `` पार्टी suites '' ).
A notable एक्सेप्शन to इस is अमीरात Stadium in London, जिससे has a पूरा टियर of club seating.
क्लबों स्तर allow fans multiple levels of entertainment.
Club स्तर seating is खोलें to the तत्व, as opposed to the entirely enclosed लक्ज़री boxes, which देता अधिक of an बाहरी छाप at roofless और open-roof stadiums और arenas.
क्लबों स्तर seating is normally bought on a अनुबंध आधार to allow for maximum लाभ on the part of the स्टेडियम.
the Club Level provides प्रशंसक with special access to an अंदर भाग of the एरिना exclusive to प्रशंसक साथ खास टिकटें.
ये क्षेत्रों हैं एयर conditioned and allow access to special restaurants, merchandise स्टैंड, और लाउंज areas of the स्टेडियम कि हैं not वरना उपलब्धियाँ.
Concession स्टैंड और विक्रेता on the Club स्तर भी often offer अलग menus than in अन्य stands to give अधिक of a special feel to the क्लबों.
ये क्षेत्रों are closed बंद to the rest of the stadium, और वे प्रायः can only be accessed through the विशेष, private क्लबों entrances.

the रूट of the eifel जलसेतु, साथ इसके औसत ढलान.
The eifel Aqueduct was one of the longest aqueducts of the रोमन साम्राज्य.
The जलसेतु, constructed in ad 80, carried जल some from the hilly Eifel region of what is अभी Germany to the ancient city of Colonia claudia आरा Agrippinensium ( present-day Cologne ).

In chemistry, a disulfide बंध ( Br.E. disulphide बंध ) is a covalent bond, usually derived by the coupling of दो thiol groups.
The linkage is also पुकारा an SS-bond or disulfide सेतु.
the overall कनेक्टिविटी is therefore r-s-s-r.
The terminology is widely used in biochemistry.
in औपचारिक terms, the कनेक्शन is a persulfide, in analogy to its congener, परऑक्साइड ( r-o-o-r ), लकिन इस शब्दावली is अस्पष्ट and is no longer used ( मगर in reference to r-s-s-h or H-S-S-H यौगिकों ).
औपचारिक चित्रण of disulfide बंध गठन as an ऑक्सीकरण.

according to the 2001 UK census, Christianity is the प्रमुख धर्म, followed by Islam, हिंदुत्व, Sikhism, Judaism and Buddhism in शर्तें of क्रमांक of adherents.

The संयुक्त Kingdom was formed by the संघ of previously स्वतंत्र देशों from 1707, और नतीजतन most of the largest धार्मिक groups do नहीं have UK-wide organisational structures.
While कुछ समूह have पृथक structures लिये the व्यक्तिगत देशों of the संयुक्त किंगडम, अन्य may have a सिंगल structure covering England and वेल्स or ग्रेट Britain.

in संयुक्त राज्य college athletics, redshirt is a विलंब or बर्खास्तगी of an खिलाड़ी 's भागीदारी in अनुक्रम to lengthen his or her period of eligibility.
Typically, a छात्र 's एथलेटिक पात्रता in a दिए sport is four सीज़न, a क्रमांक निकला from the four सालो of academic classes that are सामान्यतः जरूरी to obtain a स्नातक 's degree at an American college or university.
However, a छात्र खिलाड़ी may be offered the opportunity to redshirt लिये up to two सालो, जिससे allows the athlete to spread those four सालो of eligibility over five, or sometimes छह सालो.
in a redshirt साल, a student खिलाड़ी may attend वर्ग at the कॉलेज or university, अभ्यास साथ an athletic टोली, और dress लिये खेल लकिन he or वो may not compete during the game.
using इस mechanism, a छात्र खिलाड़ी रै up to पाँच academic years to use the चार years of eligibility, यूँ becoming a fifth-year senior.
The पद is प्रयुक्त as a verb, noun, and adjective.
लिये example, a कोच may choose to redshirt a खिलाड़ी जो is then referred to as a redshirt freshman or बस a redshirt.
The विपरीत of this is a `` true freshman. ''
संसार War i ( WWI ) थी a वैश्विक युद्ध centred in यूरोपीय कि began on 28 July 1914 और lasted जबतक 11 November 1918.
it was predominantly called the संसार युद्ध or the ग्रेट युद्ध इससे इसके occurrence जबतक the start of World युद्ध ii in 1939, and the First World युद्ध or World युद्ध I thereafter.
it शामिल all the संसार 's ग्रेट शक्तियां, जिससे यहूद समवेत in two opposing alliances : the Allies ( based on the Triple Entente of the United किंगडम, फ़्रांस और रूस ) और the सेंट्रल Powers ( originally the ट्रिपल गठबंधन of जर्मनी, austria-hungary और इटली ; लकिन, as austria–hungary था लिया the अप्रिय विरूद्ध the agreement, इटली did नहीं enter into the war ).
ये alliances यहूद दोनो reorganised and विस्तारित as अधिक राष्ट्र entered the युद्ध : इटली, जापानी और the संयुक्त States joined the allies, and the उस्मानी साम्राज्य और Bulgaria the सेंट्रल शक्तियां.
Ultimately, more than 70 million military कर्मियों, सहित 60 लाख europeans, यहूद mobilised in one of the largest युद्धों in history.
अधिक than 9 लाख combatants यहूद killed, largely because of technological advancements कि led to enormous increases in the lethality of weapons without सम्बन्धित improvements in सुरक्षा or गतिशीलता.
it थी the fifth- deadliest विरोध in world history, subsequently paving the way लिये विभिन्न political परिवर्तन, such as revolutions in many of the राष्ट्र involved.
One of the long-term कल्याणकारी of the war थी the पुनरुत्थान of साम्राज्यवाद in the विदेशी policies of the ग्रेट powers of यूरोपीय.
More तत्काल, the हत्या of archduke फ्रांज फर्डिनेंड of ऑस्ट्रिया, the वारिस to the throne of Austria-Hungary, on 28 जून 1914 by यूगोस्लाव राष्ट्रवादी Gavrilo princip in Sarajevo triggered a राजनयिक संकट जब austria-hungary subsequently वितरित an ultimatum to the किंगडम of सर्बिया.
अनेक alliances formed over the पिछला दशकों यहूद invoked.
Within weeks, the प्रमुख शक्तियां were at युद्ध and, via उनके colonies, the विरोध जल्द स्प्रेड around the world.
on 28 जुलाई, the Austro-Hungarians fired the first shots of the युद्ध as तैयारी लिये the आक्रमण of Serbia.
While the Russians mobilised, the germans invaded neutral Belgium और Luxembourg on the way to फ़्रांस, providing a casus belli for ब्रिटेन 's declaration of युद्ध विरूद्ध Germany.
After the जर्मनी कूच on पेरिस was brought to a halt—the so-called Miracle of the marne —the Western Front settled into a स्थिर बैटल of attrition with a trench लकीर that changed छोटी जबतक 1917.
on the Eastern सामने, the Russian फौज थी successful विरूद्ध the Austro-Hungarians, but थी stopped in इसके invasion of ईस्ट prussia by the Germans.
in November the Ottoman Empire joined the युद्ध, खोलने up fronts in the Caucasus, मेसोपोटामिया and the Sinai.
Italy और बुल्गारिया गई to war in 1915 and रोमानिया in 1916.
in Russia, the tsar 's government collapsed in कूच 1917 and a subsequent क्रान्ति in November brought the russians to शर्तें साथ the Central Powers.
बाद a 1918 जर्मनी offensive साथ the western सामने, the Allies drove back the germans in a श्रेणी of successful offensives और American शक्तियां began प्रवेश the trenches.
Germany, जिससे had its अपना trouble साथ क्रांतिकारियों, सहमत to an armistice on 11 नवम्बर 1918.
the युद्ध ended in विजय लिये the allies.
Events on the घर fronts यहूद as tumultuous as on the बैटल fronts, as the भागीदार tried to mobilize उनके manpower and economic संसाधन to लड़ो a कुल war.
By the समाप्त of the war, चार major इम्पीरियल powers—the German, रूसी, austro-hungarian and उस्मानी empires—ceased to exist.
the successor राज्य of the former two खोया a great amount of territory, जबकि the latter दो यहूद dismantled entirely.
the map of central यूरोपीय थी redrawn into अनेक smaller states.
The League of राष्ट्र थी formed in the आशा of preventing another ऐसे conflict.
The यूरोपीय राष्ट्रवाद शाखित by the युद्ध and the breakup of empires, the परखना of जर्मनी 's शिकस्त और problems with the सन्धि of Versailles हैं सहमत to be कारकों contributing to World युद्ध ii.
Map of countries that घोषित themselves to be socialist states अंतर्गत the Marxist–Leninist or Maoist definition - कि is to कह, `` कम्युनिस्ट states '' - between 1979 and 1983.
This period चिह्नित the greatest territorial extent of Communist states.
A communist राज्य is a राज्य where the अर्थात् of उत्पादन हैं collectively owned by the समाज.
it has a form of सरकारी characterized by single-party नियम or dominant-party rule of a communist पार्टी ( referred as तानाशाही of the proletariat by इसके proponents ) and a professed निष्ठा to a leninist or marxist–leninist विचारधारा as the guiding principle of the state.
Technically, `` communist state '' is a contradictio in terminis as a कम्युनिस्ट society as पारिभाषित by दोनो माक्र्सवादी और anarcho-communists is in principle stateless.
इससे this परिप्रेक्ष्य, the पद Marxist-Leninist state is more appropriate.
Historically, a `` communist राज्य '' referred to a प्रणाली where पब्लिक ownership of all or most means of उत्पादन by the कम्युनिस्ट पार्टी -run राज्य is deemed जरुरी to further the रूचि of the working क्लास ; today, a कम्युनिस्ट राज्य can also, लिये instance, refer to contemporary चीन और Vietnam, where a Communist Party-run राज्य exists alongside a mixed अर्थव्यवस्था.
According to marxist–leninists, the राज्य is a tool in the hands of the सत्ताधारी class, which in a socialist समाज is the working क्लास, so a समाजवादी राज्य is, according to leninists, a राज्य of the working क्लास.
in practice, कम्युनिस्ट states do नहीं actually refer to themselves as ऐसे.
वे do इस नहीं to भेस the fact that the सत्ताधारी पार्टी is कम्युनिस्ट, but rather क्युकी वे do not consider themselves to be a communist society at उपस्थित.
बजाय, they constitutionally पहचानो themselves as समाजवादी states or workers ' states.
The primary लक्ष्य of these राज्य, जिससे also explains उनके आधिकारिक नाम, is to guide their संबंधित countries in the प्रक्रम of भवन समाजवादी, ultimately leading to communism.
कम्युनिस्ट states may have अनेक विधिक राजनैतिक पार्टियों, लकिन the कम्युनिस्ट पार्टी is प्रायः granted a special or dominant भूमिका in सरकारी, प्रायः by statute or under the constitution.
नतीजतन, the institutions of the state and of the communist party become intimately entwined, such as in the विकास of समानांतर institutions.
In the 20th सदी, most communist states adopted planned economies.
however, there यहूद exceptions : the सोवियत Union during the 1920s और late 1980s और Yugoslavia बाद संसार युद्ध ii अनुमत सीमित markets and a उपाधि of कार्यकर्ता self-management, जबकि China, वियतनाम और लाओस introduced far-reaching market reforms after the 1980s.
in the 21st century, चीन और वियतनाम have allowed a मिश्रित economy to develop.
the आधारभूत अवधारणाओं of communist states often diverge from the original socio-economic ideologies from which वे develop.
As a परिणाम, अनेक adherents of ये विचारधाराओं often oppose the political systems commonly associated साथ these राज्य.
लिये उदाहरण, dissenting communists ऐसे as Trotskyists यहूद often opposed to the कम्युनिस्ट राज्य of the 20th सदी, claiming either कि वे had nothing to do with `` real '' साम्यवादी or कि the ideology of ऐसे राज्य था reached a पाइंट of अटल corruption.
माइकल Fred Phelps II ( born June 30, 1985 ) is a रिटायर्ड अमरीकी तैराक और the most decorated Olympian of सब समय, with a total of 22 medals.
Phelps also holds the all-time records लिये ओलम्पिक gold medals ( 18, दोगुना the second उच्चतम रिकार्ड holders ), ओलम्पिक gold medals in individual कार्यक्रम ( 11 ), and Olympic medals in individual कार्यक्रम for a male ( 13 ).
in जीतना eight सुनहरा medals at the 2008 Beijing खेल, फेल्प्स took the रिकार्ड लिये the most first-place finishes at any सिंगल ओलम्पिक खेल.
Five of those victories यहूद in individual कार्यक्रम, tying the सिंगल खेल रिकार्ड.
in the 2012 गर्मियाँ Olympics in London, फेल्प्स won चार golds and two चांदी medals, बनाना him the most successful athlete of the खेल for the third ओलंपिक in a पंक्ति.
फेल्प्स is the long course world recordholder in the 100-meter तितली, 200-meter butterfly और 400-meter व्यक्तिगत medley as खूब as the पूर्व long course world recordholder in the 200-meter freestyle और 200-meter व्यक्तिगत medley.
He has जीती a कुल of 71 medals in major अंतरराष्ट्रीय long-course प्रतियोगिता, 57 सुनहरा, 11 चांदी, and three bronze spanning the ओलंपिक, the World, and the पण प्रशांत championships.
फेल्प्स 's अंतरराष्ट्रीय titles and record-breaking प्रदर्शन have earned उसे the संसार Swimmer of the साल पुरस्कार seven times and अमरीकी Swimmer of the साल Award नौ टाइम्स as well as the फिना तैराक of the Year Award in 2012.
उसके unprecedented ओलम्पिक success in 2008 अर्जित Phelps खेल Illustrated magazine 's sportsman of the साल पुरस्कार.
After the 2008 गर्मियाँ ओलंपिक, Phelps प्रारंभ the माइकल Phelps न्यास, जिससे focuses on growing the sport of तैराकी and promoting healthier lifestyles.
he expects to do further कार्य with उसके न्यास बाद the 2012 ओलंपिक, जिससे he रै said होगा be उसके पिछला.
लेनोवो समूह सीमित ( ) is a Chinese multinational कंप्यूटर hardware and electronics company with इसके मुख्यालय in Beijing, China और Morrisville, उत्तर Carolina और its registered दफ्तर in हांग Kong, China.

स्लग is a common नाम for an apparently shell-less terrestrial gastropod mollusk.
the शब्द `` स्लग '' is भी प्रायः प्रयुक्त as भाग of the common name of any gastropod mollusc that रै no shell, has a बहुत घटाया शेल, or रै only a small internal शेल.
( This is in contrast to the common नाम `` snail ``, which is लागू to gastropods that have a नतीजे shell that is large पर्याप्त कि the नरम भाग of the animal can retract fully into it. )
slugs मौजूद on land और in the समुद्र, और there is even एक genus of freshwater slugs, acochlidium.
The unadorned शब्द `` slug '' is however लागू primarily to जमीन slugs, whereas slugs इससे the समुद्र or इससे freshwater हैं प्रायः referred to as `` समुद्र slugs `` और `` freshwater slugs ''.
जमीन gastropods साथ a शेल कि is not quite vestigial, लकिन is too छोटी to retract into ( जैसे अनेक in the परिवार urocyclidae ), are ज्ञात as semislugs.
the various taxonomic families of slugs form part of अनेक काफी different विकासवादी lineages which also शामिल घोंघे.
यूँ, लिये उदाहरण, the विभिन्न families of land slugs हैं नहीं very closely सम्बन्धित to एक another, despite a सतही समानता in the overall body रूप.
the shell-less कंडीशन has arisen many टाइम्स independently during the विकासवादी पास्ट, और यूँ the श्रेणी `` स्लग '' is emphatically a polyphyletic एक.
Slugs, जैसे all other gastropods, undergo torsion ( a 180° twisting of the आतंरिक अंगों ) दौरान development.
Internally, स्लग anatomy clearly shows the प्रभाव of इस rotation, लकिन externally the लाशें of land slugs appear to be more or less symmetrical, except लिये the positioning of the pneumostome, which is on एक पक्ष of the एनिमल, सामान्यतः the right हाथ side.
The नरम, slimy bodies of slugs हैं prone to desiccation, so land-living slugs हैं confined to moist environments और must रिट्रीट to damp छुपाना places when the weather is dry.
the subsequent सूचना in इस article applies to land slugs.

इम्पीरियल मानक of Napoleon i
नेपोलियन बोनापार्ट (, ; 15 अगस्त 1769 – 5 may 1821 ) थी a French सैन्य और political नेता who रोज़ to prominence दौरान the latter stages of the फ्रेंच Revolution और इसके संबद्ध wars in यूरोपीय.
As नेपोलियन i, he थी सम्राट of the French इससे 1804 to 1815.
His legal सुधार, the Napoleonic कोड, रै been a major influence on अनेक सिविल विधि jurisdictions worldwide, लकिन he is बेहतरीन remembered लिये उसके भूमिका in the युद्धों led against फ़्रांस by a श्रेणी of coalitions, the so-called napoleonic Wars.
He स्थापित आधिपत्य over most of महाद्वीपीय यूरोपीय और sought to स्प्रेड the आदर्शों of the French क्रान्ति, जबकि consolidating an इम्पीरियल monarchy जिससे restored पहलुओं of the deposed ancien Régime.
due to his success in ये wars, प्रायः विरूद्ध numerically superior दुश्मनों, he is generally regarded as एक of the महानतम सैन्य कमांडरों of सब समय, और his campaigns are पढ़ाई at सैन्य academies विश्वव्यापी.
नेपोलियन थी born at ajaccio in corsica in a family of प्रतिष्ठित इतालवी ancestry जिससे था settled corsica in the 16th सदी.
He प्रशिक्षित as an artillery officer in mainland फ़्रांस.
he rose to prominence under the French पहला गणतंत्र और led successful अभियान against the पहला and Second coalitions arrayed against France.
He led a successful आक्रमण of the इतालवी peninsula.
in 1799, he staged a तख्तापलट d'état and संस्थापित himself as पहला Consul ; पाँच years बाद the फ्रेंच सीनेट proclaimed him emperor, following a plebiscite in his पक्ष.
In the पहला दशक of the 19th सदी, the फ्रेंच साम्राज्य अंतर्गत नेपोलियन engaged in a श्रेणी of conflicts—the napoleonic युद्धों —that शामिल प्रत्येक major यूरोपीय शक्ति.
After a streak of victories, France secured a प्रबल स्थिति in continental Europe, और नेपोलियन maintained the फ्रेंच sphere of influence through the गठन of extensive alliances और the नियुक्ति of friends and family members to नियम अन्य यूरोपीय देशों as फ्रेंच क्लाएंट राज्य.
The Peninsular युद्ध और 1812 फ्रेंच invasion of रूस marked turning अंक in Napoleon 's सौभाग्य.
उसके Grande Armée थी badly damaged in the campaign और never fully बरामद.
in 1813, the छठे Coalition पराजित उसके forces at लिपजिग ; the following साल the गठबन्धन invaded France, मजबूर Napoleon to abdicate और exiled उसे to the island of एल्बा.
Less than a साल later, he escaped Elba और लौटे to शक्ति, लकिन थी पराजित at the बैटल of वाटरलू in जून 1815.
Napoleon spent the last छह years of उसके life in confinement by the अंग्रेजों on the द्वीप of संत हेलेना.
an autopsy concluded he died of पेट कर्कट, लकिन वहीँ रै महरूम some debate परिचय the cause of उसके मौत, as कुछ scholars have speculated that he was a शिकार of आर्सेनिक विषाक्तता.
This is a chronological लिस्टिंग of the संयुक्त राज्य सीनेटरों इससे पेन्सिलवेनिया.
संयुक्त States सीनेटरों are popularly elected, लिये a six-year term, शुरूआत जनवरी 3.
चुनावों हैं आयोजित the पहला मंगलवार बाद नवम्बर 1.
Before 1914, वे यहूद chosen by the पेन्सिलवेनिया General सभा, और before 1935, their terms began कूच 4.
The South Africa नेशनल rugby union team ( known as the springboks ) represents दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी in रग्बी union.
वे compete in the annual Rugby चैंपियनशिप, साथ साथ southern-hemisphere counterparts अर्जेंटीना, Australia और New Zealand.
वे have जीती this चैंपियनशिप on तीन occasions in सोलह years.
They हैं currently क्रमित second in the संसार by the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Rugby फलक, और यहूद नामित 2008 World टोली of the Year at the Laureus World Sports पुरस्कार.
Although South Africa was इंस्ट्रूमेंटल in the सृष्टि of the Rugby World कप प्रतियोगिता, the springboks did नहीं compete in the पहला दो संसार cups in 1987 और 1991 because of anti-apartheid sporting boycotts of दक्षिण Africa.
The टोली made its World कप डेब्यू in 1995, जब the newly लोकतांत्रिक दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी hosted the tournament.
The springboks तब पराजित the सब अश्वेतों 15–12 in the फाइनल, जिससे is now remembered as one of the महानतम पल in दक्षिण Africa 's sporting इतिहास, and a watershed moment in the post-apartheid nation-building प्रक्रम.
South अफ़्रीकी regained उनके शीर्षक as champions 12 years बाद, जब they defeated इंग्लैण्ड 15–6 in the 2007 फाइनल.
as a परिणाम of the 2007 World Cup टूर्नामेंट the Springboks यहूद प्रचारित to first प्लेस in the आईआरबी World rankings, a स्थिति they आयोजित जबतक जुलाई the following year जब नई जीलैंड regained the शीर्ष स्पॉट.
the springboks play in ग्रीन and सुनहरा jerseys, and their प्रतीक हैं the springbok and the protea.
the side रै been playing अंतरराष्ट्रीय rugby since 1891, जब a अंग्रेजों Isles पक्ष toured the स्वदेश, playing दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी in उनके first Test on 30 जुलाई.
दक्षिण Africa was coached by Jake White, who led the Boks to the 2007 संसार कप शीर्षक, announcing उसके इस्तीफा effectively इससे the end of 2007.
उसके replacement 's ( पीटर de villiers ) अनुबंध expired in 2011, following a 11–9 शिकस्त to ऑस्ट्रेलिया in the रग्बी संसार Cup quarter-final, जो then stated he would नहीं be signing a नई deal.
the पिछला कप्तान was जॉन smit, जो पहले he रिटायर्ड in 2011 निभाई hooker लिये सबसे of his करियर, although he रै भी महरूम a prop, mainly in 2008 and 2009.
due to smit होने अनुपलब्ध लिये the November 2010 परीक्षण after surgery, ताला विक्टर matfield took Smit 's प्लेस as कप्तान for कि tour.

The बैटल of Gettysburg (, साथ an ध्वनि ), थी लड़ा जुलाई 1–3, 1863, in और around the town of gettysburg, पेन्सिलवेनिया.
it थी the battle साथ the largest क्रमांक of हताहत in the American सिविल War and is प्रायः वर्णित as the war 's turning पाइंट.
संघ Maj. Gen. George गॉर्डन Meade 's फौज of the potomac पराजित हमले by Confederate gen. रॉबर्ट E. ली 's फौज of Northern वर्जिनिया, समाप्ति ली 's invasion of the उत्तर.
After उसके success at Chancellorsville in Virginia in May 1863, ली led his फौज through the Shenandoah घाटी to begin उसके second आक्रमण of the North—the Gettysburg Campaign.
With उसके फौज in high आत्माओं, Lee intended to shift the focus of the summer अभियान इससे war-ravaged उत्तरी वर्जिनिया and hoped to influence उत्तरी राजनेता to दे up उनके अभियोजन of the war by penetrating as far as Harrisburg, Pennsylvania, or भी Philadelphia.
prodded by अध्यक्ष Abraham lincoln, maj. gen. Joseph वेश्या स्थानांतरित his फौज in pursuit, but was relieved बस तीन दिनों before the battle और replaced by Meade.
Elements of the two armies initially collided at Gettysburg on July 1, 1863, as Lee तत्काल concentrated उसके forces there, his उद्देश्य होने to engage the Union फौज and नष्ट it.
कम ridges to the उत्तरपश्चिम of कस्बा यहूद defended initially by a संघ प्यादे division अंतर्गत ब्रिगेडियर. gen. John buford, और जल्द reinforced साथ दो corps of संघ infantry.
However, दो विशाल confederate corps फहरा them इससे the उत्तरपश्चिम and north, collapsing the hastily developed संघ लाइनों, sending the defenders retreating through the गलियों of कस्बा to the पहाड़ियाँ just to the दक्षिण.
On the दूसरी दिन of बैटल, सबसे of दोनो सेना था समवेत.
the संघ line थी रखी आउट in a रक्षात्मक formation resembling a fishhook.
In the लेट afternoon of जुलाई 2, Lee शुभारम्भ a भारी उत्पीड़न on the Union बाएँ पार्श्व, and fierce fighting raged at Little गोलाकार शीर्ष, the Wheatfield, Devil 's Den, and the आड़ू बाग़.
on the Union सही, demonstrations escalated into full-scale assaults on culp 's Hill और Cemetery हिल.
All आरपार the रणभूमि, despite significant नुकसान, the Union defenders आयोजित उनके लाइनों.
on the third दिन of बैटल, जुलाई 3, लड़ resumed on Culp 's हिल, and प्यादे लड़ाइयों raged to the ईस्ट और दक्षिण, लकिन the प्रमुख इवेंट was a dramatic infantry उत्पीड़न by 12,500 Confederates against the center of the Union line on कब्रिस्तान लकीरें, ज्ञात as Pickett 's चार्ज.
the चार्ज थी repulsed by Union rifle और तोपखाने आग, at ग्रेट नुकसान to the Confederate फौज.
ली led his army on a torturous रिट्रीट back to वर्जिनिया.
Between 46,000 and 51,000 सैनिको from both सेना were हताहत in the three-day बैटल.
That November, President Lincoln used the समर्पण ceremony लिये the Gettysburg नेशनल कब्रिस्तान to सम्मान the गिरे संघ सैनिको और redefine the purpose of the युद्ध in उसके historic gettysburg Address.
an अकादमिक discipline, or field of study, is a branch of knowledge कि is सिखाया और शोधकार्य at the कॉलेज or विश्वविद्यालयों level.
disciplines हैं पारिभाषित ( in भाग ), और recognized by the अकादमिक जर्नल्स in which research is प्रकाशित, और the सीखे societies और अकादमिक विभाग or faculties to जिससे their practitioners belong.
however, वहीँ exists no formal मापदण्ड लिये जब शैक्षणिक programs and scholarly जर्नल्स रूप an अकादमिक discipline.
a huge difference exists between, on the one hand, well स्थापित disciplines कि exist in लगभग सब universities all over the संसार, have a long history, and have a well स्थापित नियत of जर्नल्स और सम्मेलनों, और, on the अन्य hand, suggestions for नई फ़ील्ड समर्थित only by few universities and publications.
फ़ील्ड of study usually have अनेक sub-disciplines or branches, और the distinguishing lines between ये are प्रायः both मनमानी और अस्पष्ट.
PHP is a server-side एनक्रिप्शन language designed लिये वेब विकास लकिन also used as a general-purpose प्रोग्रामिंग भाषा.
PHP is now संस्थापित on अधिक than 244 लाख वेबसाइटों and 2.1 लाख वेब servers.
originally created by Rasmus Lerdorf in 1995, the reference क्रियान्वयन of PHP is अभी उत्पादित by the पीएचपी समूह.
जबकि PHP originally stood लिये निजी Home Page, it अभी स्टैंड for PHP : हाइपरटेक्स्ट Preprocessor, a recursive acronym.
PHP code is interpreted by a web सर्वर with a PHP प्रोसेसर मोड्यूल which generates the resulting वेब page : पीएचपी कमांड can be अंतःस्थापित सीधे into an HTML सोर्स दस्तावेज़ बल्कि than कॉलिंग an external file to process आंकड़ा.
It रै भी विकसित to शामिल a command-line इंटरफ़ेस काबिलियत and can be प्रयुक्त in स्टैंडअलोन graphical अनुप्रयोग.
पीएचपी is free तन्त्र released under the PHP अनुज्ञा, जिससे is incompatible with the ग्नू General Public अनुज्ञा ( जीपीएल ) due to restrictions on the usage of the term PHP.
पीएचपी can be तैनात on सबसे वेब सर्वर and भी as a स्टैंडअलोन शेल on लगभग प्रत्येक ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली and मंच, free of चार्ज.
जॉन fitzgerald `` Jack '' कैनेडी ( May 29, 1917 – नवम्बर 22, 1963 ), प्रायः referred to by his initials JFK, थी the 35th President of the संयुक्त राज्य, सेवारत from 1961 जबतक उसके death in 1963.

The Kennedy administration अपनाया the नीति of the Strategic हैमलेट कार्यक्रम जिससे थी implemented by the South वियतनामी government.
it शामिल निश्चित forced relocation, गाँव internment, and पृथक्करण of rural दक्षिण वियतनामी इससे the उत्तरी और southern कम्युनिस्ट insurgents.
Kennedy थी assassinated on नवम्बर 22, 1963 in डलास, टेक्सास.

The एफबीआई और the वारेन Commission officially concluded that Oswald was the lone assassin.
however, the United राज्य हाउस चुनें Committee on assassinations ( hsca ) concluded कि those investigations were flawed और that कैनेडी थी probably assassinated as the result of a conspiracy.
however, एबीसी News in उनके investigation, the कैनेडी हत्या : Beyond षड्यंत्र, पुष्टि the निष्कर्षों of the वारेन Commission ; having concluded Oswald acted alone.

चूंकि the 1960s information concerning कैनेडी 's private जीवन has आइये to लाइट.

A metaphor is a figure of वाक that describes a विषय by asserting कि it is, on कुछ पाइंट of तुलना, the same as another otherwise unrelated object.
रूपक is a प्रकार of सादृश्य और is closely related to अन्य rhetorical आंकड़े of speech कि achieve उनके प्रभाव via association, comparison or प्रतिरूप सहित allegory, अतिशयोक्ति, and simile.
In simpler शर्तें, a रूपक compares दो वस्तुएँ or things बगैर using the शब्द `` जैसे '' or `` as ''.
One of the most prominent उदाहरण of a metaphor in अंग्रेज़ी साहित्य is the All the संसार 's a स्टेज monologue इससे as तुम Like It :
All the world 's a स्टैगe,
और सब the men and महिलाओं merely खिलाड़ी ;
वे have उनके exits और their entrances ; — विलियम Shakespeare, as You Like It, 2/7
This quote is a रूपक क्युकी the संसार is नहीं literally a स्टेज.
By figuratively asserting कि the world is a स्टेज, शेक्सपियर उपयोग the अंक of comparison between the संसार और a stage to convey an understanding परिचय the यांत्रिकी of the world और the जीवनदान of the people भीतर it.

printmaking is the प्रक्रम of making artworks by मुद्रण, normally on पेपर.
printmaking normally covers तभी the process of बनाना prints साथ an element of मौलिकता, rather than बस होने a photographic जनन of a painting.
मगर in the मामला of monotyping, the प्रक्रम is capable of producing multiples of the वही टुकड़ा, which is called a print.
Each print produced is not माना a `` नक़ल '' but rather is माना an `` original ''.
इस is because typically each print varies to an extent due to variables intrinsic to the printmaking process, और also क्युकी the imagery of a छपाई is typically नहीं बस a reproduction of another work लकिन rather is often a unique चित्र designed इससे the start to be expressed in a particular printmaking तकनीक.
a छपाई may be ज्ञात as an छाप.
Printmaking ( अन्य than monotyping ) is नहीं चुनी only लिये इसके क्षमता to उपज multiple impressions, but rather for the unique qualities कि प्रत्येक of the printmaking प्रक्रियाओं lends itself to.
prints हैं निर्मित by transferring स्याही इससे a matrix or through a prepared स्क्रीन to a sheet of पेपर or other सामग्री.
आम प्रकार of matrices include : मेटल प्लेटों, प्रायः copper or जस्ता, or पॉलिमर plates लिये नक्काशी or etching ; स्टोन, एल्यूमिनियम, or पॉलिमर लिये lithography ; ब्लॉक of लकडी लिये woodcuts और लकडी engravings ; and linoleum लिये linocuts.
screens made of silk or synthetic fabrics हैं प्रयुक्त लिये the screenprinting process.
अन्य types of मेट्रिक्स substrates and related प्रक्रियाओं हैं discussed नीचे.
अनेक impressions मुद्रित इससे the same मेट्रिक्स रूप an edition.
Since the लेट 19th सदी, कलाकारों have generally हस्ताक्षरित individual impressions इससे an संस्करण और often number the impressions to form a सीमित संस्करण.
prints may also be printed in book form, ऐसे as illustrated किताबे or कलाकार 's books.

an interceptor वायुयान ( or simply interceptor ) is a प्रकार of fighter वायुयान designed specifically to prevent missions of enemy aircraft, विशेषकर बमवर्षक and reconnaissance aircraft, और नष्ट उन्हें, relying usually on ग्रेट गति and powerful armament.

A Vietnamese अमरीकी ( ) is an अमरीकी of वियतनामी descent.

Adolf Hitler वचनबद्ध आत्महत्या by gunshot on 30 अप्रैल 1945 in his führerbunker in बर्लिन.
His बीवी एवा ( née braun ) committed आत्महत्या साथ him by ingesting साइनाइड.
That दोपहर, in accordance with Hitler 's prior instructions, उनके remains were carried up the सीढ़ियाँ through the bunker 's आपात exit, doused in पेट्रोल and set alight in the reich chancellery garden outside the बंकर.
the सोवियत अभिलेख record that उनके जले remains यहूद recovered and interred in successive स्थितियाँ जबतक 1970 जब वे were again exhumed, cremated और the ashes बिखरे.
खाते differ as to the कारण of मौत ; एक that he died by poison तभी and another that he died by a self-inflicted gunshot, जबकि biting bas on a cyanide कैप्सूल.

एक eye-witness recorded that the body showed लक्षण of having महरूम shot through the मुँह, but this रै महरूम सिद्ध unlikely.

The दारू laws of Missouri हैं among the तनिक प्रतिबंधक and सबसे lax और permissive in the संयुक्त States.
मिसौरी is known throughout the मिडवेस्ट लिये इसके largely laissez-faire approach to दारू regulation, in शार्प कंट्रास्ट to the बहुत सख्त दारू laws of कुछ of इसके पड़ोसी, जैसे कान्सास और ओक्लाहोमा.
necrotizing fasciitis ( or ) or nf, commonly ज्ञात as flesh-eating disease or flesh-eating bacteria सिंड्रोम, is a rare संक्रमण of the deeper layers of skin और subcutaneous tissues, easily spreading across the fascial plane भीतर the subcutaneous tissue.
necrotizing fasciitis is quickly progressing, having greater risk of विकासशील in the immunocompromised due to conditions like diabetes, कर्कट, इत्यादि.
It is a कठोर बीमारी of अचानक onset और is usually treated तत्काल साथ high doses of intravenous एंटीबायोटिक.
Type I describes a polymicrobial संक्रमण, whereas प्रकार ii describes a monomicrobial infection.
अनेक प्रकार of bacteria can cause necrotizing fasciitis ( e.g., Group A streptococcus ( streptococcus pyogenes ), staphylococcus aureus, Clostridium perfringens, Bacteroides fragilis, Aeromonas hydrophila ).
ऐसे infections are अधिक likely to occur in people साथ compromised प्रतिरक्षा systems.
historically, समूह a streptococcus बना up सबसे cases of प्रकार ii infections.
however, चूंकि as early as 2001, another serious रूप of monomicrobial necrotizing fasciitis has महरूम observed साथ increasing आवृत्ति, caused by methicillin-resistant Staphylococcus aureus ( MRSA ).
कुछ प्रकाशित मामला रिपोर्ट्स have implied a possible कड़ी between उपयोग of non-steroidal anti-inflammatory drugs and NF, हालांकि the प्रमाण of the कड़ी थी कहा to be weak because of a small क्रमांक of मामला patients and it थी unclear whether the drugs just नकाबपोश the लक्षण of a secondary संक्रमण or were a cause per se.
World War II ( WWII or WW2 ), भी ज्ञात as the दूसरी संसार War, थी a global war कि lasted from 1939 to 1945.
it involved the विशाल बहुमत of the संसार 's nations —including सब of the great शक्तियां —eventually forming दो opposing सैन्य alliances : the Allies और the अक्ष.
it was the सबसे फैली युद्ध in history, साथ more than 100 million people सेवारत in सैन्य इकाई इससे over 30 different देशों.
In a राज्य of `` कुल युद्ध ``, the प्रमुख participants लगाई their संपूर्ण economic, industrial, and scientific capabilities at the सेवा of the war प्रयत्न, erasing the distinction between civilian and सैन्य संसाधन.
Marked by द्रव्यमान deaths of नागरिकों, सहित the Holocaust and the only उपयोग of नाभिकीय weapons in warfare, it resulted in 50 million to over 75 लाख fatalities.
ये deaths मेक संसार War II by दूर the deadliest विरोध in इंसान इतिहास.
the Empire of जापानी aimed to dominate East Asia और was already at war with the गणतंत्र of China in 1937, लकिन the world युद्ध is generally said to have begun on 1 सितंबर 1939 with the invasion of कैंडल by जर्मनी और subsequent घोषणाओं of युद्ध on जर्मनी by France और Britain.
From लेट 1939 to जल्दी 1941, in a श्रेणी of अभियान और treaties, जर्मनी formed the Axis alliance साथ इटली, conquering or subduing much of महाद्वीपीय यूरोपीय.
Following the molotov–ribbentrop Pact, Germany and the Soviet Union partitioned और annexed territories between themselves of उनके European पड़ोसी, सहित Poland.
the संयुक्त Kingdom and the other सदस्यों of the अंग्रेजों Commonwealth were the only major अलाइड शक्तियां continuing the fight against the Axis, साथ लड़ाइयों taking प्लेस in उत्तर अफ़्रीकी as well as the long-running बैटल of the Atlantic.
In जून 1941, the यूरोपीय अक्ष शुभारम्भ an invasion of the सोवियत Union, giving a प्रारंभ to the largest जमीन थिएटर of war in history, which tied bas the प्रमुख भाग of the Axis ' सैन्य शक्तियां लिये the बाकी of the war.
In दिसम्बर 1941, Japan joined the Axis, attacked the United States और European territories in the प्रशांत समंदर, और quickly conquered much of the पश्चिमी प्रशांत.
The Axis advance थी रोका in 1942, बाद Japan lost a series of नवल लड़ाइयों और यूरोपीय अक्ष troops यहूद defeated in North अफ़्रीकी and, decisively, at Stalingrad.
in 1943, साथ a श्रेणी of जर्मनी defeats in Eastern Europe, the Allied invasion of इटली, और अमरीकी victories in the प्रशांत, the अक्ष खोया the पहल और undertook रणनीतिक retreat on सब fronts.
In 1944, the पश्चिमी allies invaded फ़्रांस, जबकि the सोवियत संघ regained all of its territorial नुकसान और invaded Germany और its allies.
During 1944 and 1945 the संयुक्त राज्य पराजित the Japanese नेवी और captured कुंजी पश्चिमी Pacific आइलैंड्स.
the युद्ध in Europe ended with the capture of बर्लिन by सोवियत और Polish सैनिकों और the subsequent जर्मनी unconditional आत्मसमर्पण on 8 may 1945.
Following the Potsdam Declaration by the Allies on 26 July 1945, the संयुक्त States dropped परमाणु बम on the Japanese cities of हिरोशिमा on 6 अगस्त, और नागासाकी on 9 August.
साथ an आक्रमण of the Japanese archipelago imminent, and the सोवियत संघ having घोषित युद्ध on Japan by आक्रमणकारी Manchuria, जापानी surrendered on 15 August 1945, ending the युद्ध in Asia और cementing the कुल victory of the allies over the Axis.
संसार War ii altered the political संरेखण and सोशल structure of the world.
the संयुक्त राष्ट्र ( un ) थी स्थापित to foster international cooperation और prevent future विरोध.
The ग्रेट powers that यहूद the victors of the war—the संयुक्त राज्य, the सोवियत संघ, चीन, the United Kingdom, and france—became the permanent members of the संयुक्त राष्ट्र सुरक्षा परिषद.
The सोवियत Union और the United States emerged as प्रतिद्वंद्वी superpowers, setting the स्टेज for the ठंडा युद्ध, which lasted for the अगला 46 सालो.
Meanwhile, the influence of European great शक्तियां started to decline, while the decolonisation of एशिया and Africa began.
Most देशों जिनकी industries था been क्षतिग्रस्त स्थानांतरित towards आर्थिक recovery.
Political संयोजन, especially in Europe, उभरा as an प्रयत्न to stabilise postwar संबंध और लड़ो more effectively in the ठंडा युद्ध.
a सीमित देयता company ( llc ) is a लचीली form of एंटरप्राइज़ कि मिश्रणों तत्व of साझेदारी and कॉरपोरेट structures.
नोट than an llc is not a निगम, and calling an llc a निगम is technically गलत.
an llc is a विधिक रूप of कम्पनी कि provides limited देयता to इसके स्वामी in the विशाल बहुमत of संयुक्त राज्य jurisdictions.
LLCs do not need to be organized लिये profit.
Five K-Cups

K-Cup portion पैक हैं प्रयुक्त साथ Keurig or other सिंगल cup brewing प्रणालियों to काढ़ा a कप of कॉफी, tea, or hot चॉकलेट.
प्रत्येक k-cup is a plastic संग्राहक साथ a कॉफी फिल्टर inside.
मैदान coffee सेम are packed in the k-cup and sealed air-tight with a combination प्लास्टिक and foil ढक्कन.
जब the K-Cup is लगाई in a Keurig brewer, the brewer punctures the foil ढक्कन और the bottom of the k-cup and शक्तियां hot water अंतर्गत दबाव through the k-cup and into a मग.
