A chronograph is a विशिष्ट प्रकार of देखें that is प्रयुक्त as a stopwatch combined साथ a display watch.
a basic chronograph has an independent स्वीप second हाथ ; it can be प्रारंभ, रोका, और लौटे to शून्य by successive दबाव on the स्टेम.

Conventional पीसीआई ( PCI is an initialism formed from परिधीय घटक Interconnect, part of the पीसीआई लोकल बस standard और often shortened to बस पीसीआई ) is a local कंप्यूटर bus लिये attaching हार्डवेयर डिवाइस in a computer.
The पीसीआई बस supports the functions found on a processor बस, लकिन in a मानकीकृत format कि is स्वतंत्र of कोई particular प्रोसेसर.
डिवाइस कनेक्ट to the बस appear to the प्रोसेसर to be connected सीधे to the processor bus, और are आबंटित पता in the प्रोसेसर 's address space.
संलग्न devices can लो either the रूप of an integrated सर्किट fitted onto the मदरबोर्ड itself, पुकारा a planar device in the PCI specification, or an विस्तार कार्ड कि fits into a slot.
the PCI Local Bus थी पहला implemented in ibm PC compatibles, where it विस्थापित the संयोजन of isa plus एक vesa लोकल बस as the bus विन्यास.
It has subsequently been adopted लिये अन्य कंप्यूटर प्रकार.
पीसीआई और PCI-X हैं being replaced by पीसीआई एक्स्प्रेस, लकिन, most motherboards are still बना साथ एक or more पीसीआई slots, which are sufficient लिये many उपयोग.
the पीसीआई specification covers the physical आकार of the बस ( including the size और अंतरण of the सर्किट board edge electrical contacts ), विद्युत characteristics, बस समय, और प्रोटोकॉल.
the specification can be खरीदा इससे the पीसीआई Special Interest Group ( pci-sig ).
ठेठ PCI ताश used in PCs include : network ताश, ध्वनि ताश, modems, extra ports such as usb or सीरियल, tv tuner ताश और डिस्क controllers.
PCI video cards replaced ISA और vesa cards, until growing बैंडविड्थ आवश्यकताएँ outgrew the capabilities of PCI ; the पसन्दीदा interface for वीडियो ताश became अगप, and तब PCI Express.
PCI वीडियो ताश remain उपलब्धियाँ for उपयोग साथ old PCs बगैर AGP or PCI एक्स्प्रेस स्लॉट.
अनेक devices previously provided on पीसीआई expansion cards हैं now commonly integrated onto motherboards or उपलब्धियाँ in universal सीरियल बस और पीसीआई Express संस्करण.
माइकल Whitaker स्मिथ ( born October 7, 1957 ) is an अमरीकी contemporary ईसाई संगीतकार, who रै charted primarily in the contemporary ईसाई and occasionally in the मुख्यधारा चार्ट.

स्मिथ is a three-time Grammy पुरस्कार विजेता, और रै अर्जित 40 dove Awards.
Over the कोर्स of his career, he sold अधिक than 13 लाख albums and recorded 29 No. 1 hit songs, fourteen सुनहरा एल्बम, and five प्लेटिनम एल्बम.
स्मिथ is an अमरीकी म्यूज़िक पुरस्कार प्राप्तकर्ता ; he was भी named one of People पत्रिका 's `` Most खूबसूरत लोगों ''.
An अमरीकी poster इससे the World युद्ध ii -era that थी used to inform people परिचय what वे should do if they suspect तोड़फोड़.
तोड़फोड़ is a deliberate action aimed at weakening another एंटिटी through subversion, obstruction, disruption, or destruction.
in a workplace सेटिंग, sabotage is the conscious withdrawal of दक्षता generally directed at causing some change in workplace शर्तें.
एक जो engages in तोड़फोड़ is a saboteur.
as a नियम, saboteurs try to छिपाते उनके पहचान क्युकी of the consequences of उनके actions.
For example, whereas an पर्यावरणीय pressure group might be happy to be identified with an act of तोड़फोड़, it होता नहीं want the individual पहचान of the perpetrators known.

the history of टेलीविज़न comprises the कार्य of numerous इंजीनियर्स and inventors in several countries over अनेक दशकों.
The earliest प्रस्ताव was in 1908, in a पेपर by A. A. Campbell-Swinton and postulated the use of cathode rays.
the first व्यावहारिक demonstrations of टेलीविज़न, however, यहूद developed using electromechanical methods to scan, संचारण, and reproduce an image.
As electronic camera और प्रदर्शक tubes यहूद perfected, electromechanical टेलीविज़न दिया रास्ता to all-electronic प्रणालियों in nearly सब applications.

lyme बीमारी, lyme borreliosis is an संक्रामक बीमारी caused by at least three प्रजाति of जीवाणु belonging to the genus borrelia.
borrelia burgdorferi sensu stricto is the main कारण of lyme disease in उत्तर अमेरिका, whereas borrelia afzelii and Borrelia garinii कारण सबसे European cases.
the बीमारी is नामित बाद the कस्बों of lyme और Old Lyme, Connecticut, यूएसए, जहाँ a क्रमांक of cases यहूद पहचाना in 1975.
हालांकि Allen steere एहसास कि lyme बीमारी थी a tick-borne बीमारी in 1978, the कारण of the बीमारी remained a mystery until 1981, when B. burgdorferi was identified by विली burgdorfer.
lyme disease is the most common tick-borne बीमारी in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध.
borrelia is transmitted to humans by the काटना of संक्रमित ticks belonging to a few species of the genus Ixodes ( `` hard ticks '' ).
जल्दी लक्षण may शामिल fever, headache, थकान, अवसाद, और a characteristic गोलाकार skin rash पुकारा erythema migrans ( em ).
बाएँ अनुपचारित, बाद symptoms may involve the joints, दिल, and सेंट्रल बेचैन प्रणाली.
In सबसे cases, the संक्रमण और its symptoms हैं eliminated by antibiotics, especially if the बीमारी is treated early.
Delayed or अपर्याप्त उपचार can lead to more गंभीर symptoms, जिससे can be disabling and मुश्किल to treat.

शिश्न ( plural penises or penes ) is a सामान्य पद लिये the organs साथ जिससे male और उभयलिंगी animals introduce शुक्राणु into receptive महिलाओं दौरान copulation.
ऐसे organs occur in अनेक पशु, दोनो vertebrate और invertebrate, but males do नहीं bear a penis in every एनिमल प्रजाति, and in those प्रजाति in which the पुरूष करता bear a so-called penis, the penes in the various species are not necessarily समजात.
लिये example, the शिश्न of a स्तनधारी is at सबसे analogous to the शिश्न of a पुरूष insect or barnacle.
The पद शिश्न applies to many reproductive intromittent organs, but नहीं to सब ; लिये example the intromittent अंग of most cephalopoda is the hectocotylus, a specialised arm, और male spiders उपयोग उनके pedipalps.
in most प्रजाति of पशु in जिससे there is an organ कि might reasonably be वर्णित as a penis, it रै no प्रमुख फलन अन्य than intromission, or at least conveying the sperm to the female, लकिन in the placental स्तनधारियों the शिश्न bears the distal part of the urethra, which discharges दोनो मूत्र दौरान urination और semen during copulation as the अवसर requires.
Artists और रंगमंडल ( a & R ) is the प्रभाग of a रिकार्ड लेबल or म्यूज़िक publishing कम्पनी कि is responsible लिये हुनर scouting and overseeing the कलाकारी विकास of रिकॉर्डिंग artists and/or songwriters.
It भी अधिनियमों as a liaison between कलाकारों और the रिकार्ड label or publishing कम्पनी ; every कार्यकलाप involving कलाकारों to the पाइंट of एल्बम release is generally माना under the purview of, और जिम्मेदारी of, a & r.
A furlong is a measure of distance in इम्पीरियल इकाई and u.S. प्रथागत units बराबर to one-eighth of a mile, equivalent to 220 गज, 660 फीट, 40 rods, or 10 जंजीरों.
the सटीक मान of the furlong varies थोड़ा among english-speaking देशों.
पाँच furlongs हैं लगभग 1 kilometre ( 1.0058 km is a closer approximation ).
चूंकि the असली परिभाषा of the मीटर थी one-quarter of one ten-millionth of the परिधि of the धरती ( साथ the ग्रेट circle coincident साथ the meridian of देशांतर passing through Paris ), the circumference of the Earth is about 40,000 km or about 200,000 furlongs.

Lithium batteries are डिस्पोजेबल ( primary ) batteries that have लिथियम मेटल or lithium यौगिकों as an anode.
वे stand अलावा इससे अन्य batteries in उनके ऊँची चार्ज density ( long life ) और ऊँची लागत प्रति ईकाई.
depending on the डिज़ाइन and रासायनिक यौगिकों used, lithium कोशिकाएं can उपज voltages इससे 1.5 V ( comparable to a zinc–carbon or क्षारीय battery ) to परिचय 3.7 V. लिथियम बैटरी हैं widely used in उत्पाद such as portable consumer इलेक्ट्रॉनिक डिवाइस.

Facebook is an online सोशल नेटवर्किंग service, जिनकी नाम stems from the colloquial name लिये the किताब given to विद्यार्थी at the start of the अकादमिक साल by some विश्वविद्यालयों administrations in the संयुक्त States to सहायता विद्यार्थी मिलेंगी to know each अन्य.
it थी founded in फ़रवरी 2004 by चिह्नित zuckerberg साथ उसके कॉलेज roommates and fellow Harvard विश्वविद्यालयों विद्यार्थी Eduardo Saverin, Andrew mccollum, Dustin moskovitz और क्रिस ह्यूजेस.
the जालस्थल 's सदस्यता थी initially limited by the founders to हार्वर्ड विद्यार्थी, but थी विस्तारित to other colleges in the Boston area, the आइवी लीग, और Stanford विश्वविद्यालयों.
It gradually added support लिये विद्यार्थी at विभिन्न अन्य universities पहले opening to ऊँची school विद्यार्थी, और eventually to anyone aged 13 और over.
Facebook now allows कोई users जो घोषित themselves to be at तनिक 13 years बूढ़ा to become पंजीकृत users of the साईट.
Users जरूर पंजीकरण पहले using the साईट, बाद जिससे they may create a personal profile, add अन्य users as friends, और exchange messages, including automatic notifications when वे अद्यतन their प्रोफ़ाइल.
Additionally, उपयोक्ता may जुड़ें common-interest user समूह, organized by कार्यस्थल, स्कूल or college, or अन्य विशेषताएँ, and categorize उनके friends into सूचियाँ such as `` People इससे Work '' or `` Close Friends ''.
As of सितंबर 2012, Facebook has over one billion क्रियाशील उपयोक्ता.
according to a May 2011 Consumer रिपोर्ट्स सर्वेक्षण, वहीँ हैं 7.5 लाख children अंतर्गत 13 with accounts और 5 लाख अंतर्गत 10, violating the साईट 's शर्तें of सेवा.
In may 2005, accel साझेदार invested $ 12.7 लाख in Facebook, and जिम breyer added $ 1 लाख of उसके own money to the घट.

अर्विन Johannes eugen ख़बरों ( 15 नवम्बर 1891 – 14 अक्तूबर 1944 ), popularly ज्ञात as the मरुस्थल फॉक्स ( wüstenfuchs, ), was a जर्मनी फ़ील्ड Marshal of World War ii.
he अर्जित the आदर of both his own सैनिकों and the enemies he fought.
ख़बरों was a highly decorated officer in संसार War I और थी awarded the Pour le Mérite लिये उसके कारनामे on the Italian front.
In संसार युद्ध II, he further विशिष्ट खुद as the commander of the 7th panzer Division during the 1940 invasion of फ़्रांस.
उसके leadership of जर्मनी और इतालवी forces in the उत्तर अफ़्रीकी अभियान स्थापित उसे as एक of the most समर्थ commanders of the war, और earned उसे the appellation of the मरुस्थल फॉक्स.
he is regarded as one of the सबसे skilled कमांडरों of मरुस्थल warfare in the विरोध.
he later commanded the जर्मनी शक्तियां opposing the अलाइड cross-channel आक्रमण in Normandy.
उसके कार्यभार never took उसे to the पूर्वी सामने.
ख़बरों is regarded as having been a दयालु and पेशेवर अधिकारी.
His afrika Korps थी never अभियुक्त of युद्ध crimes, और soldiers captured दौरान his अफ़्रीकी campaign were reported to have been treated humanely.
आदेश to मार यहूदी soldiers, नागरिकों और captured कमांडो यहूद उपेक्षित.
Late in the war, Rommel थी linked to the षड्यंत्र to assassinate Adolf हिटलर.
चूंकि Rommel was a national नायिका, Hitler desired to eliminate him quietly.
he forced Rommel to कमिट suicide with a cyanide गोली, in return for assurances that ख़बरों 's परिवार होता नहीं be persecuted following his मौत.

Earth दिन is an annual event, मनाये on अप्रैल 22, on जिससे कार्यक्रम हैं आयोजित विश्वव्यापी to demonstrate support for environmental सुरक्षा.
it was पहला celebrated in 1970, और is अभी coordinated globally by the Earth दिन Network, और मनाये in अधिक than 192 देशों प्रत्येक साल.
In 1969 at a युनेस्को सम्मेलन in San फ्रांसिस्को, the तिथि प्रस्तावित थी कूच 21, 1970, the पहला day of वसन्त in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध.
This दिन of प्रकृति 's equipoise was बाद मंजूर in a Proclamation signed by Secretary सामान्य u Thant at the संयुक्त Nations.
A month later a पृथक धरती दिन was संस्थापित by संयुक्त राज्य सीनेटर gaylord Nelson as an पर्यावरणीय teach-in first आयोजित on अप्रैल 22, 1970.
नेल्सन was बाद awarded the Presidential Medal of Freedom Award in मान्यता of उसके work.

आयोडीन is a रासायनिक element with symbol i and atomic क्रमांक 53.
the नाम is from यूनानी ioeidēs, अर्थ violet or purple, due to the color of elemental आयोडीन vapor.
आयोडीन और its यौगिकों हैं primarily used in पोषण, और industrially in the production of एसिटिक एसिड और निश्चित polymers.
Iodine 's अपेक्षाकृत high atomic क्रमांक, कम toxicity, और ease of attachment to सशुल्क यौगिकों have बना it a भाग of many x-ray contrast सामग्री in आधुनिक आयुर्विज्ञान.
Iodine has तभी one stable समस्थानिक.
a number of आयोडीन radioisotopes हैं भी used in medical अनुप्रयोग.
Iodine is found on धरती mainly as the highly water-soluble आयोडाइड आयन, I−, जिससे concentrates it in महासागर और brine तालों.
जैसे the other हैलोजन्स, free iodine occurs mainly as a diatomic अणु i2, और तब only momentarily बाद होने oxidized from आयोडाइड by an oxidant जैसे फ़्री ऑक्सीजन.
in the ब्रह्मांड and on Earth, आयोडीन 's high atomic number makes it a अपेक्षाकृत rare तत्व.
However, its presence in समंदर water has दिए it a भूमिका in जीवविज्ञान.
It is the अधिकतम अनिवार्य element utilized widely by life in biological functions ( तभी टंगस्टन, employed in enzymes by a few species of bacteria, is heavier ).
आयोडीन 's rarity in अनेक soils, due to initial low प्रचुरता as a crust-element, और भी leaching of घुलनशील आयोडाइड by rainwater, रै led to many deficiency समस्याएं in land animals and अंतर्देशीय इंसान populations.
Iodine deficiency affects about two billion लोगों and is the अग्रणी preventable कारण of बौद्धिक disabilities.
Iodine is required by उच्चतर पशु, जिससे उपयोग it to synthesize thyroid हार्मोन, which contain the element.
Because of इस फलन, radioisotopes of आयोडीन हैं concentrated in the थायराइड ग्रंथि साथ साथ nonradioactive iodine.
if inhaled, the radioisotope iodine-131, which has a high fission उत्पाद yield, concentrates in the thyroid, but is easily remedied with पोटैशियम iodide उपचार.
lobbying ( भी lobby ) is the अधिनियम of attempting to influence decisions बना by officials in the सरकारी, सबसे प्रायः legislators or members of regulatory एजेंसियों.
lobbying is done by many अलग types of people and organized groups, including individuals in the private sector, corporations, fellow विधायक or government officials, or वकालत groups ( ब्याज समूह ).
lobbyists may be among a विधायक 's constituencies, अर्थ a वोटर or bloc of मतदाता भीतर उसके or उसके electoral ज़िला, or नहीं ; वे may engage in lobbying as a कारोबार, or not.
पेशेवर lobbyists हैं लोगों whose business is trying to influence विधान on निमित्त of a समूह or व्यक्तिगत who hires them.
individuals और nonprofit संगठन can भी lobby as an अधिनियम of volunteering or as a छोटी part of their normal जॉब ( लिये उदाहरण, a CEO बैठक साथ a प्रतिनिधि about a project महत्वपूर्ण to his/her company, or an activist meeting with his/her विधायक in an unpaid capacity ).
Governments प्रायः define और regulate organized समूह lobbying कि रै become influential.
the आचार and नैतिकता of lobbying are.
lobbying is often बोला of साथ contempt, जब the implication is कि लोगों साथ inordinate socioeconomic शक्ति are corrupting the विधि ( टेढ़ी it दूर from fairness ) in अनुक्रम to serve उनके own conflict of interest.
But another पक्ष of lobbying is बनाना sure कि others ' interests are विधिवत defended विरूद्ध others ' corruption, or भी simply बनाना यकीनन कि अल्पसंख्यक रूचि हैं fairly defended विरूद्ध mere tyranny of the बहुमत.
For उदाहरण, a चिकित्सा संघ, or a trade संघ of स्वास्थ्य insurance companies, may lobby a विधानमंडल in अनुक्रम to counteract the influence of तम्बाकू companies, in which मामला the lobbying होता be viewed by सबसे people as जायज ( विधिवत defending विरूद्ध अन्य ' भ्रष्टाचार ).
the difficulty in drawing उद्देश्य लाइनों between जिससे lobbyists हैं `` शुभ lobbyists '' और जिससे ones are `` ख़राब ones '' is compounded by the cleverness साथ जिससे lobbyists or उनके क्लाइंट can argue कि their अपना lobbying is of the `` good '' kind.
At दिल, the प्रयत्न to influence विधान is a शक्ति संघर्ष.
as in other forms of शक्ति संघर्ष, such as war or law प्रवर्तन, motives range इससे to self-defense to fighting लिये इंसाफ, and the dividing line between predation और इंसाफ is विषय to rationalization.

Cream यहूद a 1960s British चट्टान supergroup consisting of bassist/vocalist जोकर ब्रूस, guitarist/vocalist eric क्लैप्टन, और drummer अदरक बेकर.
उनके sound was characterised by a संकर of ब्लूज़ चट्टान, मुश्किल rock and साइकेडेलिक चट्टान, combining the psychedelia-themed गीत, eric क्लैप्टन 's ब्लूज़ गिटार playing और vocals, जोकर Bruce 's voice और prominent बास playing and अदरक बेकर 's जैज़ -influenced drumming.
the group 's तीसरा एल्बम, Wheels of Fire, was the संसार 's पहला platinum-selling दोगुना album.
मलाई हैं widely regarded as being the संसार 's पहला कामयाब supergroup.
in उनके करियर, वे बेची over 15 million albums विश्वव्यापी.
Cream 's म्यूज़िक शामिल गीतों आधारित on परंपरागत ब्लूज़ ऐसे as `` Crossroads `` and `` spoonful ``, और आधुनिक ब्लूज़ ऐसे as `` Born Under a ख़राब चिह्न ``, as खूब as more eccentric गीतों such as `` Strange काढ़ा ``, `` Tales of वीर ulysses `` and `` Toad ``.
Cream 's biggest हिट्स यहूद `` I महसूस फ़्री `` ( uk, क्रमांक 11 ), `` सनशाइन of Your प्रेम `` ( us, क्रमांक 5 ), `` श्वेत Room `` ( US, क्रमांक 6 ), `` क्रॉसरोड्स '' ( US, क्रमांक 28 ), और `` बैज `` ( uk, क्रमांक 18 ).
मलाई बना a significant प्रभाव on the लोकप्रिय म्यूज़िक of the समय, और, साथ साथ जिमि हेंड्रिक्स, और टेरी कठ of शिकागो, popularised the उपयोग of the wah-wah pedal.
वे provided a heavy yet technically proficient musical theme कि foreshadowed और बहकावे the emergence of अंग्रेजों bands ऐसे as the जेफ़ Beck समूह in the लेट 1960s.
the बैंड 's live performances बहकावे प्रगतिशील चट्टान acts such as Rush.
मलाई यहूद inducted into the चट्टान और फेंकें हॉल of कीर्ति in 1993.
वे यहूद included in दोनो Rolling स्टोन और VH1 's lists of the `` 100 महानतम कलाकारों of All Time ''.
They were also क्रमित number 16 on vh1 's `` 100 Greatest Artists of Hard Rock ''.
Hairspray is a 1988 कॉमेडी फिल्मी लिखा and directed by John waters, और starring ricki झील, Sonny बोनो, डिब्बी Harry, माइकल st. जेरार्ड, shawn थॉम्पसन, Colleen Fitzpatrick, जेरी stiller, और in his last फिल्मी भूमिका, दैवी.
hairspray was a dramatic प्रस्थान इससे waters ' पहले works, साथ a much broader intended दर्शक.
in fact, Hairsprays pg is the mildest rating a Waters फिल्मी has received ; सबसे of उसके पिछला films यहूद रेटेड x by the MPAA.
नियत in 1962 Baltimore, मेरीलैंड, the फिल्मी revolves around self-proclaimed `` pleasantly plump '' किशोरावस्था Tracy turnblad as वो pursues स्टारडम as a नर्तकी on a लोकल tv show और rallies विरूद्ध जातिगत segregation.
Hairspray थी तभी a moderate कामयाबी upon इसके initial theatrical रिलीज, earning a modest सकल of $ 8 लाख.
However, it प्रबंधित to आकर्षित a larger दर्शक on home video in the early 1990s and became a cult classic.

A Christian denomination is an identifiable religious body अंतर्गत a common नाम, ढांचा, and doctrine भीतर christianity.
Some groups included do नहीं consider themselves a denomination ( e.g., the Catholic Church considers itself the एक true गिरिजाघर और the अपोस्टोलिक देखिए, और as pre-denominational ).
कुछ समूह viewed by non-adherents as denominational actively resist होने पुकारा a denomination और do not have कोई formal denominational structure, authority, or record-keeping परे the local congregation ; अनेक groups within बहाली गति पतन into इस श्रेणी.
कुछ groups are विशाल ( e.g. catholics, Lutherans, Anglicans or baptists ), जबकि अन्य are just a few छोटी churches, और in सबसे मामले the relative आकार is नहीं evident in this list.
आधुनिक movements ऐसे as Fundamentalist christianity, Pietism, Evangelicalism, pentecostalism and the पवित्रता गति sometimes cross denominational lines, or in कुछ cases create new denominations out of two or अधिक continuing groups, ( as is the case for many United और uniting चर्च, for उदाहरण ).
Such subtleties और complexities are नहीं clearly चित्रित here.
प्रमुख विभाजन within christianity.
नोट : This is नहीं a complete सूची, लकिन aims to provide a comprehensible overview of the विविधता among denominations of Christianity.
as वहीँ are reported to be approximately 41,000 Christian denominations, अनेक of which can नहीं be सत्यापित to be significant, only those denominations साथ विकिपीडिया आलेख होगा be listed in अनुक्रम to ensure कि सब प्रविष्टियां on इस सूची हैं notable और verifiable.
Between denominations, theologians, और तुलनात्मक religionists there are considerable disagreements परिचय which groups can be properly पुकारा Christian, मतभिन्नता arising primarily इससे doctrinal मतभेद between groups.
For the purpose of simplicity, इस सूची is intended to प्रतिबिंबित the self-understanding of प्रत्येक denomination.
स्पष्टीकरण of different राय concerning उनके औकात as ईसाई denominations can be मिला at उनके respective आलेख.
वहीँ is no official मान्यता in most parts of the संसार for धार्मिक bodies, and वहीँ is no आधिकारिक clearinghouse जिससे could determine the status or respectability of धार्मिक bodies.
Often वहीँ is considerable disagreement between विभिन्न churches परिचय whether अन्य churches should be labeled with pejorative शर्तें ऐसे as `` cult '', or परिचय whether इस or कि समूह enjoys कुछ माप of respectability.
Such considerations प्रायः vary इससे प्लेस to प्लेस, जहाँ एक religious group may enjoy बहुमत status in one प्रदेश, लकिन be widely regarded as a `` खतरनाक cult '' in another भाग of the संसार.
समावेश on इस सूची करता नहीं indicate कोई निर्णय परिचय the आकार, महत्व, or अक्षर of a समूह or इसके members.
1804 मैप of `` louisiana ``, edged on the वेस्ट by the Rocky Mountains.
The Louisiana खरीदें ( `` बिक्री of Louisiana '' ) was the अधिग्रहण by the संयुक्त राज्य of America in 1803 of of फ़्रांस 's अर्जी to the territory of Louisiana.
the U.S. सशुल्क 50 लाख francs ( $ 11,250,000 ) प्लस रद्दीकरण of debts worth 18 लाख francs ( $ 3,750,000 ), लिये a total sum of 15 million dollars ( less than 3 cents प्रति acre ) for the louisiana territory ( $ लाख in डॉलर, कम than 42 सेंट प्रति एकड़ ).
The louisiana territory encompassed सब or भाग of 15 present u.S. राज्य and two Canadian provinces.
the land purchased contained सब of present-day अरकंसास, मिसौरी, आयोवा, ओक्लाहोमा, कान्सास, and नेब्रास्का ; भाग of मिनेसोटा कि were वेस्ट of the मिसिसिपी नदी ; सबसे of North डकोटा ; सबसे of दक्षिण डकोटा ; northeastern नई Mexico ; उत्तरी Texas ; the portions of मोंटाना, व्योमिंग, and कोलोराडो east of the महाद्वीपीय divide ; louisiana west of the मिसिसिपी River, सहित the city of New Orleans ; और small portions of land that would आखिरकार become भाग of the Canadian provinces of अलबर्टा and Saskatchewan.
फ़्रांस नियंत्रित इस vast क्षेत्रफल from 1699 जबतक 1762, the साल it gave the territory to इसके ally स्पेन.
अंतर्गत नेपोलियन बोनापार्ट, France took back the territory in 1800 in the hope of building an साम्राज्य in North अमेरिका.
a slave विद्रोह in Haiti और an impending war साथ ब्रिटेन, however, led फ़्रांस to abandon ये plans और sell the संपूर्ण territory to the United States, who था originally intended तभी to seek the खरीदें of नई Orleans और इसके सटा lands.
the खरीदें of the territory of louisiana took प्लेस दौरान the प्रेसिडेंसी of थामस Jefferson.
at the time, the खरीदें faced घरेलू opposition क्युकी it थी thought to be असंवैधानिक.

A लीग is a ईकाई of length ( or, rarely, area ).
it थी long common in Europe और Latin America, लकिन it is no longer an आधिकारिक ईकाई in कोई स्वदेश.
the लीग originally referred to the अलहदा a person could चलना in an घंटा.
Since the Middle आयु, अनेक values have been निर्दिष्ट in अनेक countries.
in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of nautical दूरियाँ, the 3 मील ( 4.8 km ) अलहदा corresponds to कैसा दूर an observer of average ऊँचाई ( 5'9 '' or 1.78 m ) can देखिए when खड़ा at sea level.
यूँ, a ship traveling one `` लीग '' रै पहुँचे what थी previously the farthest visible अलहदा on the क्षितिज.
the lack of a ऐतिहासिक और वैश्विक standard लिये the exact माप of a `` लीग '' can be accounted for by the variable elevation of the निरीक्षक ( i.e., sightings from a ship 's deck vs. masthead ).
the Irish राज्य आए into being in 1922 as the Irish फ़्री राज्य, a dominion of the अंग्रेजों Commonwealth, having seceded इससे the United किंगडम अंतर्गत the anglo-irish सन्धि.
it comprises 26 of Ireland 's 32 काउंटी.
चूंकि 1949 it has existed as the Republic of Ireland.
इससे इसके न्यास, the आयरिश Free State थी embroiled in a सिविल war between राष्ट्रवादियों supporting the Treaty और opponents जो समर्थित a गणतंत्र.
the pro-Treaty पक्ष, संगठित as cumann na nGaedheal उभरा victorious इससे the conflict और won subsequent elections.
वे formed the सरकारी of the राज्य until 1932, when वे peacefully handed over power to the anti-Treaty faction in fianna Fáil, जो defeated उन्हें in an election.
the Irish state, despite इसके violent beginnings, has remained a उदार लोकतंत्र throughout इसके existence.
a new संविधान in 1937 removed अनेक of the कड़ी with Britain स्थापित अंतर्गत the सन्धि और Ireland 's neutrality in the दूसरी संसार War demonstrated its स्वतंत्रता in foreign policy matters इससे ब्रिटेन.
In 1948 आयरलैंड formally left the अंग्रेजों Commonwealth और अपनाया the शीर्षक of `` Republic ''.
in the economic गोला, the आयरिश राज्य has had a मिश्रित प्रदर्शन.
on स्वतंत्रता, it थी एक of the wealthier देशों in Europe per head of population.
however it also inherited from अंग्रेजों rule the समस्याएं of बेरोजगारी, emigration, uneven भौगोलिक विकास और कमी of a native industrial आधार.
For much of इसके history, the राज्य struggled to rectify these समस्याएं.
Particular peaks of करणों were अंकित दौरान the लेट 1930s, 1950s and 1980s, when the आयरिश अर्थव्यवस्था अंकित little विकास.
in the 1930s, fianna fáil सरकारें attempted to create आयरिश domestic उद्योग using subsidies और सुरक्षात्मक tarifs.
in the लेट 1950s, these नीतियों यहूद dropped in पक्ष of free व्यापार साथ चयनित countries और encouraging of foreign investment साथ low taxes.
इस थी विस्तारित when आयरलैंड entered the European आर्थिक Community in 1972.
in the 1990s and 2000s, Ireland अनुभवी an आर्थिक बूम ज्ञात as the सेल्टिक बाघ, in जिससे the country 's GDP surpassed अनेक of इसके यूरोपीय पड़ोसी.
Immigration भी surpassed emigration, bringing the राज्य 's जनसांख्यिकी up to over 4 लाख.
however, चूंकि 2008, आयरलैंड has experienced a कठोर crisis in the बैंकिंग सेक्टर और साथ sovereign कर्ज़.
the resultant economic slump has deepened the प्रभाव of the संसार recession on आयरलैंड.
इससे 1937 to 1998, the आयरिश संविधान शामिल a claim on उत्तरी आयरलैंड as a भाग of the नेशनल territory.
however, the राज्य also opposed and प्रयुक्त its सुरक्षा forces against those armed समूह - principally the Provisional Irish Republican फौज, जो tried to एकजुट आयरलैंड by फ़ोर्स.
इस occurred in the 1950s, throughout the 1970s and 1980s और रै जारी on a घटाया scale.
आयरिश सरकारें meanwhile आजमाया to दलाली an agreement to the विरोध ज्ञात as the Troubles within उत्तरी Ireland इससे 1968 to the लेट 1990s.
the अंग्रेजों सरकारी officially recognised the सही of the आयरिश सरकारी to be a party to the Northern negotiations in the Anglo-Irish Agreement of 1985.
in 1998, as भाग of the शुभ Friday अनुबंध, the आयरिश संविधान थी altered by referendum to हटाएँ the territorial claim to उत्तरी Ireland और instead extend the सही of Irish नागरिकता to all the people of the island should वे wish to have it.
जॉन क्विंसी एडम्स ( July 11, 1767february 23, 1848 ) थी the छठे अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य ( 1825–1829 ).
he परोसा as अमरीकी diplomat, सीनेटर, और Congressional प्रतिनिधि.
he थी a member of the federalist, Democratic-Republican, नेशनल रिपब्लिकन, और later anti-masonic और Whig पार्टियों.
Adams was the बेटे of पूर्व President John एडम्स and Abigail एडम्स.
As a diplomat, Adams played an महत्वपूर्ण भूमिका in negotiating many अंतरराष्ट्रीय treaties, सबसे notably the Treaty of ghent, which ended the War of 1812.
As Secretary of राज्य, he negotiated साथ the संयुक्त Kingdom over America 's northern border साथ Canada, negotiated साथ Spain the annexation of Florida, and authored the मुनरो doctrine.
Historians agree he was एक of the greatest राजनयिकों और secretaries of राज्य in अमरीकी history.
as president, he sought to modernize the American economy और प्रचारित education.
Adams enacted a भाग of उसके agenda and paid off much of the national कर्ज़.
he थी stymied by a Congress controlled by his enemies, और उसके lack of patronage संजाल helped politicians eager to undercut उसे.
He खोया उसके 1828 bid for re-election to Andrew Jackson.
In doing so, he became the first अध्यक्ष चूंकि his पिता to serve a single पद.
Adams is best known as a diplomat जो तराशा अमेरिका 's विदेशी नीति in लकीर साथ उसके ardently nationalist commitment to अमेरिका 's republican मान.
More recently Howe ( 2007 ) portrayed एडम्स as the exemplar and moral leader in an era of modernization.
During Adams ' lifetime, technological नवप्रवर्तनों and नई अर्थात् of communication स्प्रेड संदेश of धार्मिक revival, social सुधार, and party politics.
goods, money, और लोगों traveled अधिक rapidly और efficiently than कभी पहले.
एडम्स थी निर्वाचित a U.S. प्रतिनिधि from Massachusetts बाद leaving दफ्तर, सेवारत for the पिछला 17 सालो of उसके जीवन साथ far वृहद acclamation than he था achieved as अध्यक्ष.
He is, so दूर, the तभी अध्यक्ष later elected to the United राज्य हाउस of Representatives ( though John Tyler was elected to the हाउस of Representatives of the Confederate राज्य just पहले उसके death in 1862 ).
Animated by his growing revulsion विरूद्ध slavery, एडम्स became a leading प्रतिद्वन्दी of the स्लेव Power.
he predicted कि if a civil war यहूद to break आउट, the अध्यक्ष could abolish गुलामी by using उसके युद्ध शक्तियां.
Adams भी पूर्वानुमानित the Union 's dissolution over the गुलामी समस्या, लकिन said that if the South became स्वतंत्र वहीँ होता be a श्रेणी of खूनी स्लेव revolts.

It थी released to the पब्लिक on कूच 14, 2011.

रेस is a वर्गीकरण system used to categorize humans into large and distinct populations or groups by anatomical, सांस्कृतिक, जातीय, जेनेटिक, geographical, ऐतिहासिक, भाषाई, religious, or social संबद्ध.
पहला प्रयुक्त to denote नेशनल संबद्धों, the term began to be प्रयुक्त to सुनाना to शारीरिक traits in the 17th सदी.
in the जल्दी 20th century the पद थी प्रायः used, in a taxonomic भाव, to denote genetically differentiated इंसान populations defined by phenotype.
जबकि biologists sometimes use the अवधारणा of रेस to मेक भेद among फजी सेट of traits, others in the वैज्ञानिक community suggest कि the विचार of race प्रायः is used in a भोली or simplistic way, i.e. कि among इंसानो, रेस has no taxonomic significance : all living humans belong to the वही प्रजाति, Homo sapiens and subspecies, Homo sapiens sapiens.
Social conceptions and groupings of races vary over time, involving लोक taxonomies
that define of individuals आधारित on आभास traits.
वैज्ञानिकों consider biological essentialism obsolete, and generally discourage जातिगत explanations for सामूहिक differentiation in both शारीरिक और behavioral traits.
Since the second half of the 20th सदी the associations of रेस साथ the ideologies and theories कि grew आउट of the work of 19th-century anthropologists and physiologists रै led to the use of the शब्द रेस itself becoming समस्यापूर्ण.
हालांकि still used in general contexts, it is now often replaced by अन्य words जिससे हैं less अस्पष्ट और emotionally charged, ऐसे as populations, people ( s ), जातीय समूह or communities depending on context.
लुसी स्टोन ( अगस्त 13, 1818 – October 19, 1893 ) थी a prominent American abolitionist और suffragist, and a vocal एडवोकेट and आयोजक promoting अधिकारों लिये women.
In 1847, Stone became the first स्त्री इससे मैसाचुसेट्स to earn a कॉलेज उपाधि.
वो spoke आउट लिये महिलाओं 's अधिकारों and विरूद्ध गुलामी at a time when women यहूद हतोत्साहित और prevented इससे public speaking.
स्टोन थी the first recorded अमरीकी स्त्री to retain उसके अपना पिछला name after marriage.
Stone 's organizational activities for the कारण of women 's अधिकारों yielded tangible gains in the difficult राजनैतिक environment of the 19th सदी.
Stone helped initiate the पहला नेशनल महिलाओं 's अधिकारों Convention और she supported और sustained it annually साथ with a number of other लोकल, राज्य और क्षेत्रीय activist conventions.
Stone spoke in सामने of a क्रमांक of legislative लाशें to promote कानून giving अधिक rights to women.
She assisted in establishing the Woman 's नेशनल वफ़ादार लीग to सहायता pass the Thirteenth amendment और thereby abolish गुलामी, बाद जिससे वो helped form the largest समूह of like-minded महिलाओं 's rights reformers, the नीतियां मॉडरेट अमरीकी स्त्री suffrage संघ, which worked लिये दशकों at the state स्तर in favor of women 's सही to vote.
Stone wrote extensively परिचय a चौड़ी range of women 's rights, publishing और distributing speeches by herself and अन्य, and सम्मेलन proceedings.
In the long-running and influential Woman 's जर्नल, a साप्ताहिक periodical कि she स्थापित और प्रचारित, स्टोन aired दोनो her अपना and differing views परिचय women 's rights.
Called `` the orator '' and `` the morning स्टार of the स्त्री 's rights movement '', स्टोन delivered a वाक जिससे sparked सुसान B. एंथोनी to take up the cause of महिलाओं 's suffrage.
Elizabeth Cady stanton लिखा that `` लुसी स्टोन थी the first person by जिसको the दिल of the American public थी deeply stirred on the स्त्री question. ''
साथ, एंथोनी, stanton, और Stone have been called the 19th century `` triumvirate `` of महिलाओं 's suffrage and feminism.
In वित्त, a बंध is an यंत्र of indebtedness of the बंध issuer to the holders.
It is a कर्ज़ security, अंतर्गत which the जारीकर्ता owes the धारकों a कर्ज़ and, depending on the terms of the बंध, is obliged to अदा उन्हें interest ( the कूपन ) or to repay the प्रिंसिपल at a later तिथि, termed the maturity.
Interest is प्रायः payable at fixed intervals ( semiannual, सालाना, sometimes मासिक ).
बहुत प्रायः the bond is परक्राम्य, i.e. the ownership of the यंत्र can be transferred in the secondary मार्केट.
यूँ a बंध is a रूप of ऋण or iou : the होल्डर of the बंध is the lender ( creditor ), the issuer of the bond is the borrower ( debtor ), and the coupon is the ब्याज.
bonds provide the borrower with बाह्य निधि to finance long-term investments, or, in the मामला of सरकारी bonds, to finance current व्यय.
प्रमाणपत्र of जमा ( CDs ) or छोटी पद वाणिज्यिक paper are माना to be धन मार्केट instruments और नहीं bonds : the प्रमुख अंतर is in the length of the पद of the instrument.
bonds और stocks हैं both प्रतिभूति, लकिन the major अंतर between the दो is that ( पूंजी ) stockholders have an इक्विटी stake in the company ( i.e. they हैं owners ), whereas bondholders have a creditor हिस्सेदारी in the कम्पनी ( i.e. वे हैं lenders ).
another अंतर is कि bonds प्रायः have a पारिभाषित पद, or परिपक्वता, बाद जिससे the bond is redeemed, whereas stocks may be बकाया indefinitely.
An एक्सेप्शन is an irredeemable bond, such as Consols, which is a perpetuity, i.e. a बंध with no maturity.

A स्केल मॉडल is a शारीरिक मॉडल, a representation or नक़ल of an ऑब्जेक्ट कि is larger or smaller than the actual size of the ऑब्जेक्ट, which seeks to maintain the सापेक्ष proportions ( the scale factor ) of the physical आकार of the original ऑब्जेक्ट.
बहुत प्रायः the स्केल मॉडल is प्रयुक्त as a मार्गदर्शिका to बनाना the object in full आकार.
स्केल मॉडल are निर्मित or एकत्रित लिये many कारण.
the Zune hd was a portable मीडिया player in the zune product family released on सितंबर 15, 2009 by Microsoft.
It was a सीधा competitor साथ the ठहराना ipod and iPhone श्रेणी of मोबाईल devices.
It was initially released in 16 and 32 gb capacities.
a 64 gb संस्करण was released on April 9, 2010.

निष्पादन by electrocution, प्रायः performed using an इलेक्ट्रिक chair, is an निष्पादन method originating in the संयुक्त राज्य in which the condemned व्यक्ति is strapped to a specially निर्मित wooden chair and electrocuted through electrodes placed on the देह.
इस execution विधि थी created by employees of थामस Edison दौरान the War of Currents, and has महरूम used तभी in the United राज्य और, लिये a काल of several decades, in the फिलीपीन ( its पहला use वहीँ in 1924 under अमरीकी occupation, पिछला in 1976 ).
historically, एकबार the condemned person was संलग्न to the chair, विभिन्न चक्र ( differing in voltage और duration ) of alternating वर्तमान would be passed through the व्यक्तिगत 's देह, in अनुक्रम to कारण fatal damage to the आतंरिक अंगों ( सहित the brain ).
the first jolt of इलेक्ट्रिक वर्तमान थी designed to कारण immediate unconsciousness और brain death ; the दूसरी एक थी designed to कारण fatal क्षति to the vital organs.
Death was अक्सर caused by विद्युत overstimulation of the दिल.
Although in the United States the इलेक्ट्रिक कुर्सी has become a symbol of the मौत दंड, इसके उपयोग is in मनाही due to the वृद्धि of lethal इंजेक्शन, which is widely believed to be a अधिक humane method of निष्पादन.
हालांकि some राज्य still maintain electrocution as a method of निष्पादन, आज it is only कायम as a द्वितीयक method that may be चुनी over lethal injection at the request of the prisoner.
as of 2010, electrocution is an वैकल्पिक रूप of निष्पादन in Alabama, Florida, दक्षिण कैरोलिना और वर्जिनिया.
They allow the कैदी to चुनें lethal इंजेक्शन as an वैकल्पिक विधि.
in the states of केंटकी और टेनेसी, the इलेक्ट्रिक chair has महरूम retired मगर लिये those whose पूंजी crimes यहूद वचनबद्ध prior to legislated तिथियाँ in 1998 ( केंटकी : कूच 31, 1998 ; Tennessee : दिसम्बर 31, 1998 ) and who chose electrocution.
in दोनो राज्य, inmates जो do नहीं choose electrocution or inmates जो वचनबद्ध उनके अपराधों after the designated तिथि are killed by lethal इंजेक्शन.
the इलेक्ट्रिक chair is an वैकल्पिक रूप of execution approved for संभावित use in अरकंसास and ओक्लाहोमा if अन्य फ़ॉर्म of execution हैं found असंवैधानिक in the राज्य at the time of निष्पादन.
it is the sole विधि of execution in Vermont, where treason is the तभी capital अपराधों.
On फ़रवरी 8, 2008, the नेब्रास्का परम् Court determined कि निष्पादन by इलेक्ट्रिक chair was a `` cruel और unusual punishment '' under the राज्य 's संविधान.
इस brought executions of इस type to an end in नेब्रास्का, the तभी बाकी state to retain electrocution as its एकमात्र विधि of निष्पादन for murder.
The Maryland हाउस of Delegates is the निम्नतर house of the सामान्य सभा, the राज्य legislature of the American State of Maryland, and is रचित of 141 delegates निर्वाचित इससे 47 districts.
The हाउस of delegates कक्ष is स्तिथ in the Maryland State हाउस ( state कैपिटल ) on राज्य Circle in annapolis, जिससे is the राज्य पूंजी.

the मुक्ति of Paris ( भी known as the बैटल for Paris ) took प्लेस during संसार युद्ध ii इससे 19 अगस्त 1944 until the आत्मसमर्पण of the occupying जर्मनी garrison on 25 अगस्त.
the Liberation of पेरिस प्रारंभ साथ an uprising by the French प्रतिरोध विरूद्ध the जर्मनी गैरीसन.
on 24 August, the फ्रेंच Forces of the आंतरिक ( शक्तियां françaises de l'intérieur, FFI ) प्राप्त सुदृढीकरण इससे the Free French फौज of मुक्ति और from the U.S. तीसरा फौज अंतर्गत General Patton.
The capital प्रदेश of फ़्रांस था महरूम governed by Nazi Germany चूंकि the हस्ताक्षर of the Second Compiègne armistice in जून 1940, जब the German फौज occupied उत्तरी और westernmost France, and जब the puppet शासन of Vichy France थी स्थापित in the कस्बा of vichy in सेंट्रल फ़्रांस.
This बैटल marked the मुक्ति of Paris and the निर्वासन of the vichy सरकारी to sigmaringen in Germany.
however, वहीँ थी स्टिल much heavy लड़ to be किया पहले फ़्रांस was liberated, सहित the अभियान in दक्षिणी फ़्रांस दौरान august-september ( in Provence और extending into the southwestern प्रदेश of the Vosges kyu ), साथ the german-held seaports of western फ़्रांस ( ऐसे as at brest और dunkirk ), in alsace और लोरेन in पूर्वी फ़्रांस, and in northeastern फ़्रांस, such as साथ the Rhine और Moder नदियाँ.
The जर्मनी फौज और SS लड़ा doggedly in these areas लिये the remainder of 1944 और into 1945.
`` Feelin ' alright ? '' भी known as `` Feeling alright '' is a सोंग लिखा by Dave Mason of the अंग्रेज़ी चट्टान बैंड ट्रैफ़िक from उनके eponymous 1968 एल्बम, ट्रैफ़िक.

Sample view of an इलेक्ट्रॉनिक health record आधारित on images
Sample view of an electronic स्वास्थ्य रिकार्ड
An इलेक्ट्रॉनिक स्वास्थ्य रिकार्ड ( ehr ) is an evolving अवधारणा पारिभाषित as a systematic संग्रहण of electronic स्वास्थ्य information परिचय व्यक्तिगत मरीजों or populations.
it is a record in digital स्वरूप कि is theoretically सक्षम of being shared across अलग health परवाह जमावट.
in कुछ मामले इस sharing can occur by way of network-connected enterprise-wide सूचना systems और other सूचना networks or exchanges.
ehrs may include a दायरा of आंकड़ा, including जनसांख्यिकी, चिकित्सा इतिहास, medication और allergies, immunization औकात, प्रयोगशाला test परिणाम, radiology images, vital लक्षण, personal stats जैसे age and weight, and billing information.
ऋण origination is the प्रक्रम by which a borrower applies for a new ऋण, और a lender प्रक्रियाओं that अनुप्रयोग.
Origination generally शामिल all the steps from लेने a ऋण application up to disbursal of funds ( or घटती the application ).
Loan सर्विसिंग कवर सबकुछ बाद disbursing the funds जबतक the loan is fully सशुल्क बंद.
ऋण origination is a specialized version of नई account opening लिये financial services संगठन.
निश्चित people और organizations specialize in loan origination.
Mortgage brokers और other बंधक originator कंपनियाँ serve as a prominent उदाहरण.
वहीँ हैं many different प्रकार of लोन.
लिये अधिक सूचना on loan types, देखिए the loan and उपभोक्ता lending articles.
Steps शामिल in originating a loan vary by loan type, various kinds of loan रिस्क, regulator, lender नीति, और अन्य factors.
Top left : the टेनेसी घाटी प्राधिकार, भाग of the नई सौदे, being signed into विधि in 1933.
शीर्ष सही : फ्रैंकलिन Delano Roosevelt, who was responsible लिये initiatives और programs collectively ज्ञात as the नई सौदे.
नीचे : a public mural इससे एक of the कलाकारों employed by the नई सौदे.
the New Deal थी a series of आर्थिक कार्यक्रम enacted in the संयुक्त राज्य between 1933 and 1936.
वे शामिल अध्यक्षीय executive orders or कानून passed by कॉंग्रेस दौरान the पहला पद of अध्यक्ष फ्रैंकलिन D. रूज़वेल्ट.
The programs were in जवाब to the Great अवसाद, और केन्द्रित on what इतिहासकारों call the `` 3 rs '' : Relief, रिकवरी, और सुधार.
That is Relief for the unemployed और poor ; रिकवरी of the economy to सामान्य levels ; and सुधार of the वित्तीय प्रणाली to prevent a repeat अवसाद.
The New Deal produced a राजनैतिक realignment, making the Democratic Party the majority ( as well as the party कि held the White हाउस for सात आउट of नौ Presidential शर्तें from 1933 to 1969 ), साथ इसके base in उदार विचार, the श्वेत दक्षिण, परंपरागत Democrats, बिग city मशीने, और the newly empowered मजदूर संघ और जातीय अल्पसंख्यकों.
the Republicans were विभाजित, साथ conservatives opposing the entire New सौदे as an दुश्मन of कारोबार और growth, और liberals accepting some of it and promising to मेक it अधिक कुशल.
The realignment crystallized into the New सौदे गठबन्धन कि वर्चस्व most अध्यक्षीय elections into the 1960s, while the विपक्ष Conservative गठबन्धन largely नियंत्रित Congress इससे 1937 to 1963.
by 1936 the पद `` liberal '' typically was used लिये supporters of the New Deal, and `` conservative `` for its opponents.
इससे 1934 to 1938, Roosevelt थी assisted in his endeavours by a “pro-spender” majority in कॉंग्रेस ( drawn from two-party, प्रतिस्पर्धी, non-machine, प्रगतिशील, और बाएँ पार्टी जिले ).
As noted by सिकंदर हिक्स, “Roosevelt, समर्थित by विरल, non-southern डेमोक्रेट majorities — 270 non-Southern डेमोक्रेट प्रतिनिधि और 71 non-southern डेमोक्रेट senators — spelled दूसरी नई सौदे reform.”
अनेक इतिहासकारों फर्क between a `` पहला New सौदे '' ( 1933–34 ) and a `` दूसरी नई Deal '' ( 1935–38 ), साथ the दूसरी one more liberal और अधिक विवादास्पद.
The `` First New Deal '' ( 1933–34 ) dealt साथ diverse समूह, इससे banking and railroads to industry and खेती, सब of जिससे demanded सहायता for economic survival.
the Federal आपात राहत प्रशासन, लिये instance, provided $ 500 लाख लिये राहत परिचालन by states and शहरों, जबकि the short-lived cwa ( Civil Works प्रशासन ) दिया बस्तियों धन to operate make-work प्रोजेक्ट in 1933-34.
The `` दूसरी New Deal `` in 1935–38 included the वेगनर Act to प्रचार मजदूर संघ, the works Progress प्रशासन ( WPA ) राहत कार्यक्रम ( जिससे made the संघीय सरकारी by दूर the largest सिंगल employer in the nation ), the सोशल सुरक्षा अधिनियम, और नई कार्यक्रम to सहायता tenant farmers और migrant workers.
the फाइनल major items of New सौदे legislation यहूद the सृष्टि of the संयुक्त राज्य आवास प्राधिकार और Farm सुरक्षा प्रशासन, दोनो in 1937, और the Fair मजदूर Standards Act of 1938, जिससे नियत अधिकतम घंटों and न्यूनतम मजदूरी for सबसे श्रेणी of workers.
the आर्थिक downturn of 1937–38, and the कड़वा split between the afl और CIO मजदूर unions led to प्रमुख Republican gains in कॉंग्रेस in 1938.
रूढ़िवादी republicans और Democrats in कॉंग्रेस joined in the अनौपचारिक रूढ़िवादी गठबन्धन.
by 1942–43 वे shut bas राहत programs such as the wpa और ccc और अवरोधित प्रमुख उदार proposals.
Roosevelt खुद turned his ध्यान to the war प्रयत्न, और won reelection in 1940 और 1944.
the Supreme अदालत घोषित the National रिकवरी प्रशासन ( nra ) and the पहला संस्करण of the agricultural Adjustment Act ( AAA ) असंवैधानिक, however the aaa थी rewritten and then upheld.
As the first रिपब्लिकन अध्यक्ष निर्वाचित after fdr, ड्वाइट D. आइज़नहावर ( 1953–61 ) बाएँ the नई Deal largely intact, even expanding it in कुछ areas.
in the 1960s, Lyndon B. जॉनसन 's Great समाज used the नई सौदे as प्रेरणा for a नाटकीय विस्तार of उदार कार्यक्रम, which रिपब्लिकन रिचर्ड M. Nixon generally retained.
After 1974, however, the कॉल लिये deregulation of the अर्थव्यवस्था gained bipartisan support.
the नई Deal विनियमन of banking ( glass–steagall Act ) थी निलंबित in the 1990s.
अनेक नई Deal programs remain क्रियाशील, साथ कुछ स्टिल ऑपरेटिंग अंतर्गत the असली names, सहित the Federal जमा Insurance Corporation ( fdic ), the Federal क्रॉप Insurance Corporation ( fcic ), the संघीय Housing प्रशासन ( FHA ), और the टेनेसी Valley प्राधिकार ( TVA ).
the largest programs स्टिल in अस्तित्व आज हैं the सोशल सुरक्षा प्रणाली और the प्रतिभूति and एक्सचेंज Commission ( सेक ).
a स्त्री ( ), pl : women ( ) is a female इंसान.
The पद स्त्री is usually reserved for an वयस्क, साथ the पद लड़की होने the usual term लिये a female child or adolescent.
However, the पद स्त्री is also sometimes प्रयुक्त to identify a female इंसान, regardless of age, as in वाक्यांश ऐसे as `` महिलाओं 's अधिकारों ``.

हालांकि नहीं प्रयुक्त by the बहुमत of the संसार 's countries, daylight saving समय is common in the पश्चिमी संसार.
daylight saving time ( DST ) —also गर्मियाँ समय in British अंग्रेज़ी — is the practice of advancing घड़ियाँ दौरान the हल्का months so कि evenings have more daylight और mornings have कम.
typically clocks are adjusted आगे one hour निकट the प्रारंभ of spring and are समायोजित backward in autumn.
the आधुनिक विचार of daylight saving थी पहला proposed in 1895 by जार्ज vernon हडसन and it थी first implemented दौरान the पहला संसार युद्ध.
अनेक देशों have used it at विभिन्न टाइम्स चूंकि तब.
much of the United States प्रयुक्त DST in the 1950s and 1960s, and DST उपयोग विस्तारित following the 1970s energy crisis and रै been widely प्रयुक्त in उत्तर America and यूरोपीय since तब.
The practice has been दोनो praised और criticized.
Adding daylight to evenings लाभ retailing, खेल, and other क्रियाएँ that exploit धूप after working घंटों, लकिन can cause समस्याएं लिये evening entertainment and अन्य occupations tied to the sun.
हालांकि an जल्दी लक्ष्य of dst थी to reduce संध्या usage of incandescent lighting ( formerly a प्राथमिक use of electricity ), modern हीटिंग और कूलिंग उपयोग patterns differ greatly, and research about how dst currently affects energy use is सीमित or contradictory.
DST clock शिफ्ट उपस्थित अन्य चुनौतियां.
वे complicate timekeeping, and can disrupt बैठक, सफर, billing, record keeping, medical डिवाइस, भारी उपकरण, and नींद पैटर्न.
तन्त्र can प्रायः समायोजन कंप्यूटर घड़ियाँ automatically, लकिन इस can be सीमित और error-prone, विशेषकर जब dst dates are changed.

Montargis is a commune in the loiret department in north-central France on the loing नदी.

in कंप्यूटर storage, a लॉजिकल ईकाई क्रमांक, or LUN, is a number प्रयुक्त to पहचानो a लॉजिकल ईकाई, which is a यंत्र addressed by the SCSI प्रोटोकॉल or प्रोटोकॉल which encapsulate scsi, ऐसे as Fibre चैनल or iscsi.

Though not technically correct, the पद `` lun '' is often भी प्रयुक्त to refer to the लॉजिकल डिस्क itself.
the इन्जील according to चिह्नित (,, to euangelion kata Markon ), commonly shortened to the इन्जील of चिह्नित or बस Mark, is the second book of the नई वसीयत.
इस canonical खाता of the जीवन of Jesus of Nazareth is one of the तीन synoptic gospels.
it थी thought to be an निचोड़, which accounts लिये इसके place as the second gospel in the Bible.
However, most contemporary scholars now लिहाज़ it as the earliest of the canonical gospels ( c 70 ).
That चिह्नित थी used as a सोर्स लिये the अन्य synoptic gospels इन्जील of मैथ्यू और इन्जील of ल्यूक is widely held by अनेक, हालांकि not सब, नई Testament विद्वानों.
The इन्जील of Mark narrates the Ministry of यीशु इससे his baptism by John the बैपटिस्ट to his मौत और क़यामत.
It focuses particularly on the पिछला सप्ताह of उसके life ( chapters 11–16 ) in जेरूसलम.
इसके स्विफ्ट कथा portrays यीशु as a वीर man of कार्रवाई, an exorcist, healer and चमत्कार worker.
An important थीम of Mark is the मुक्तिदाता रहस्य.
यीशु silences the demoniacs he heals, कोशिशें unsuccessfully to रखना his मुक्तिदाता पहचान secret, और conceals his संदेश साथ parables.

सबसे विद्वानों believe that the असली text of the इन्जील ends at चिह्नित 16:8 साथ the discovery of यीशु ' खाली मकबरा and that the following खाता of उसके resurrection appearances is a बाद जोड.
According to परंपरा और कुछ early गिरिजाघर writers, the लेखक is चिह्नित the Evangelist, the साथी of the apostle पीटर.
the gospel, however, appears to rely on अनेक underlying स्त्रोत, varying in रूप और in theology, which tells विरूद्ध the परंपरा that the इन्जील was based on पीटर 's preaching.
the टेक्स्ट is a संकलन जिससे may शामिल eye-witness accounts as खूब as ज्ञात अपोस्टोलिक preachings, and pre-existing लिखा रिकॉर्ड कि do नहीं मौजूद आज but can be पुष्टि from 2nd-century commentators.
Some of the stories in the इन्जील may have महरूम transmitted orally before होने written bas.
विभिन्न तत्व भीतर the gospel suggest that the लेखक wrote in सीरियाई or फिलिस्तीन for a non-Jewish ईसाई community.

The story began as a sequel to tolkien 's 1937 children 's काल्पनिक अनोखा The होब्बिट, but eventually विकसित into a much larger work.

it is the दूसरी best-selling अनोखा कभी लिखा, साथ over 150 million copies बेची.

The कार्य थी initially intended by tolkien to be one आवाज़ of a two-volume नियत, साथ the अन्य होने The Silmarillion, लकिन इस विचार थी dismissed by his प्रकाशक.

The three volumes यहूद entitled the Fellowship of the रिंग, The दो मीनारें, and the Return of the किंग.

the रब of the बजती has चूंकि been reprinted numerous टाइम्स और अनूदित into many भाषाएं.
tolkien 's कार्य has महरूम the subject of extensive विश्लेषण of its themes और origins.
Although a प्रमुख कार्य in itself, the स्टोरी थी only the last गति of a larger एपिक tolkien था worked on since 1917, in a प्रक्रम he described as mythopoeia.

The रब of the बजती in its turn is माना to have had a ग्रेट effect on आधुनिक काल्पनिक ; the प्रभाव of tolkien 's works is such that the उपयोग of the words `` tolkienian '' और `` tolkienesque '' have महरूम अंकित in the Oxford अंग्रेज़ी शब्दकोष.

in the नेशनल Football League, training camp refers to the time before the ऋतु commences.
दौरान इस समय, टीमों होगा sometimes congregate at an outside location, usually a विश्वविद्यालयों, to conduct प्रशिक्षण camp लिये at तनिक the पहला few weeks.
This is समान to baseball 's spring प्रशिक्षण.
प्रशिक्षण camp is प्रयुक्त in several अलग तरीके.
नई खिलाड़ी और कोच use it to acclimate themselves to new teammates and प्रणालियों.
लिये younger खिलाड़ी, it serves as a period of evaluation ; for दिग्गजों, it is समय to round वापस into form.
प्रशिक्षण camp is divided into अनेक different components.
The पहला is scrimmages.
ये are pseudo-games where टीमों चलाएं nearly full खेल ' लायक of plays.
Sometimes, दो practice sessions are held on the same day.
This अवधारणा is referred to as two-a-days.
अन्य भाग of training शिविर शामिल drills, बैठक with coaches और other players at एक 's स्थिति, वज़न प्रशिक्षण, और pre-season games.
the latter हाफ of training camp leads directly into the exhibition season.
With NFL प्रशिक्षण शिविरों starting in late-july, the biggest concern has महरूम निर्जलीकरण.
In 2001, Minnesota Vikings player Korey Stringer died of a चिकित्सा कंडीशन आधारित इससे dehydration और heatstroke.
the death of Stringer prompted the एनएफएल to बदलें their training policies.
At प्रत्येक practice, प्रत्येक team जरूर have the टोली डॉक्टर and प्रशिक्षकों on the फ़ील्ड ; additionally, an एम्बुलेंस जरूर be उपस्थित दौरान practices.

In 2002, a Cleveland भूरा प्रदर्शनी खेल ended due to बिजली निकट Cleveland भूरा स्टेडियम, और कठोर storms have महरूम known to disrupt प्रशिक्षण शिविरों.

In computing, a संचिका प्रणाली ( or filesystem ) is a प्रकार of data स्टोर जिससे can be प्रयुक्त to store, retrieve और update a नियत of फाइलें.
The term could refer to the अमूर्त आंकड़ा structures प्रयुक्त to define files, or to the वास्तविक तन्त्र or फर्मवेयर components कि implement the अमूर्त विचार.
Some file प्रणालियों हैं प्रयुक्त on लोकल data भंडार डिवाइस ; अन्य provide संचिका access via a network protocol ( e.g. NFS, SMB, or 9p क्लाइंट ).
Some संचिका systems हैं `` आभासी '', in कि the `` files '' supplied are computed on request ( e.g. procfs ) or are merely a मानचित्रण into a different संचिका प्रणाली प्रयुक्त as a बैकिंग store.
the संचिका system manages अभिगम to both the सामग्री of files and the metadata about those फाइलें.
It is responsible लिये arranging storage स्पेस ; विश्वसनीयता, efficiency, and tuning साथ लिहाज़ to the शारीरिक भंडार medium are महत्वपूर्ण डिज़ाइन considerations.
William Howard taft ( September 15, 1857 – कूच 8, 1930 ) was the 27th अध्यक्ष of the United States ( 1909–1913 ) and बाद the दसवाँ मुख्य इंसाफ of the संयुक्त States ( 1921–1930 ).
he is the तभी person to have परोसा in both of ये कार्यालयों.
पहले बनने अध्यक्ष, Taft, a Republican, थी चयनित to serve on the श्रेष्ठ Court of Cincinnati in 1887.
In 1890, Taft was appointed solicitor सामान्य of the संयुक्त States और in 1891 a न्यायधीश on the संयुक्त States अदालत of Appeals लिये the छठे सर्किट.
In 1900, अध्यक्ष William McKinley appointed taft Governor-General of the फिलीपीन.
In 1904, President थियोडोर रूज़वेल्ट नियुक्त taft सचिव of युद्ध in an effort to दूल्हे Taft, तब उसके close राजनैतिक ally, into his handpicked presidential successor.
taft assumed a prominent role in problem solving, assuming on कुछ अवसरों the role of एक्टिंग सचिव of State, while घटती दोहराया offers इससे Roosevelt to serve on the परम् अदालत.
Riding a वेव of popular support लिये fellow रिपब्लिकन Roosevelt, taft जीती an easy विजय in उसके 1908 bid लिये the presidency.
In उसके only term, Taft 's domestic कार्यसूची emphasized trust-busting, सिविल सेवा सुधार, strengthening the अंतरराज्यीय कॉमर्स Commission, improving the प्रदर्शन of the डाक service, and ड्योढ़ी of the Sixteenth amendment.
विदेश, taft sought to further the आर्थिक development of राष्ट्र in लैटिन अमेरिका और एशिया through `` Dollar कूटनीति ``, and दिखाया decisiveness और restraint in जवाब to क्रान्ति in मैक्सिको.
the task-oriented taft थी बेख़बर to the political ramifications of उसके decisions, प्रायः alienated his अपना key constituencies, and was overwhelmingly पराजित in उसके बोली लिये a दूसरी पद in the अध्यक्षीय चुनाव of 1912.
in सर्वेक्षण of अध्यक्षीय scholars, taft is प्रायः क्रमित near the middle of lists of सब अमरीकी राष्ट्रपतियों.
बाद leaving दफ्तर, Taft खर्च his time in academia, arbitration, and the ढूंढें for संसार peace through उसके self-founded League to enforce Peace.
in 1921, after the First World War, अध्यक्ष वारेन G. हार्डिंग नियुक्त taft मुख्य Justice of the United States.
taft served in this capacity until shortly before his मौत in 1930.

Louisville (, or ) is a प्रमुख city और the largest नगर in the U.S. राज्य of Kentucky and the county सीट of जेफरसन काउंटी.

a कूलिंग नहाना, in प्रयोगशाला chemistry ( often लकिन not सदा सशुल्क रसायन ) practice, is a liquid मिश्रण जिससे is प्रयुक्त to maintain low temperatures, typically between 13 °C और −196 °C.
These कम temperatures are प्रयुक्त to collect liquids after आसवन, to remove solvents using a rotary evaporator, or to perform a रासायनिक reaction नीचे रूम तापमान ( देखिए : गतिज कंट्रोल ).
कूलिंग baths हैं generally एक of दो प्रकार : ( a ) a ठंडा द्रव ( विशेषकर द्रव nitrogen, जल, or भी air ) — लकिन सबसे commonly the पद refers to ( b ) a mixture of 3 components : ( 1 ) a cooling agent ( ऐसे as शुष्क ice or जल ice ) ; ( b ) a द्रव 'कैरीr ' ( such as liquid जल, ethylene glycol, एसीटोन, etc. ), जिससे transfers ऊष्मा between the नहाना और the पोत ; ; and ( c ) an योगात्मक to depress the melting-point of the solid/liquid system.
( a परिचित उदाहरण of this is the उपयोग of an ice/rock-salt मिश्रण to फ्रीज बर्फ cream.
the phase-change of ice into liquid जल requires energy, 'pulling ' heat from the system.
Adding नमक lowers the अस्थायी at जिससे इस happens, meaning अधिक energy रै to be अवशोषित from the पर्यावरण in अनुक्रम to melt the बर्फ.
इस effectively makes the ice 'colder ' — it जरूर 'pull ' अधिक ऊष्मा इससे इसके environment to become liquid. )
खाने disorders हैं conditions पारिभाषित by असामान्य खाने habits that may involve either अपर्याप्त or excessive food intake to the detriment of an व्यक्तिगत 's physical और दिमागी health.
Bulimia नर्वोज़ा और anorexia nervosa हैं the सबसे आम specific फ़ॉर्म in the United किंगडम.
अन्य types of खाने disorders शामिल binge खाने विकार और eating disorder नहीं otherwise निर्दिष्ट.
bulimia nervosa is a विकार characterized by binge eating और purging.
Purging can शामिल self-induce उल्टी, over-exercising, and the usage of diuretics, enemas, and laxatives.
Anorexia नर्वोज़ा is characterized by चरम खाना restriction to the point of self-starvation और excessive वज़न घाटा.
Though primarily विचार of as affecting females ( an estimated 5–10 million होने प्रभावित in the u.K. ), eating विकार affect males as खूब.
an estimated 10 – 15 % of लोगों साथ खाने disorders हैं males ( Gorgan, 1999 ).
( an estimated 1 लाख u.K. males होने प्रभावित ).
Although eating विकार are increasing सब over the संसार among दोनो मेन and women, वहीँ is प्रमाण to suggest कि it is महिलाओं in the Western संसार जो are at the highest रिस्क of विकासशील them and the degree of westernization increases the रिस्क.
Nearly half of all अमेरिकी personally जान किसी with an खाने विकार.
The कौशल to comprehend the सेंट्रल प्रक्रियाओं of भूख रै increased tremendously चूंकि लेप्टिन थी discovered, and the कौशल to observe the कृत्यों of the brain as well.
Interactions between motivational, homeostatic and self-regulatory कंट्रोल प्रक्रियाओं are शामिल in eating आचरण, which is a कुंजी component in eating disorders.
The precise cause of eating disorders is not entirely समझा, लकिन वहीँ is प्रमाण कि it may be linked to other चिकित्सा शर्तें और परिस्थितियों.
सांस्कृतिक idealization of thinness and youthfulness have contributed to खाने disorders affecting विविध populations.
एक study दिखाया कि girls साथ adhd have a वृहद मौका of getting an खाने विकार than those नहीं affected by ADHD.
Another पढ़ाई सुझाया कि महिलाओं साथ PTSD, especially due to sexually सम्बन्धित trauma, हैं more संभावित to develop anorexia नर्वोज़ा.
एक study showed कि foster girls are अधिक संभावित to develop bulimia नर्वोज़ा.
कुछ think कि peer दबाव and idealized body-types seen in the मीडिया हैं भी a significant factor.
कुछ शोध show that लिये certain लोगों वहीँ are जेनेटिक कारण क्यों वे may be prone to विकासशील an eating विकार.
Recent studies have found evidence a सहसंबंध between patients साथ bulimia नर्वोज़ा and substance use विकार.
in addition, चिंता disorders and personality विकार हैं common occurrences with क्लाइंट of खाने विकार.
जबकि proper उपचार can be अत्यधिक effective for many suffering इससे विशिष्ट types of खाने disorders, the consequences of eating disorders can be कठोर, सहित मौत ( whether इससे direct चिकित्सा प्रभाव of अशांत खाने habits or from comorbid conditions ऐसे as suicidal thinking ).
Slavery in the संयुक्त राज्य existed इससे the early years of the औपनिवेशिक काल ; it was firmly स्थापित by the time the United राज्य sought स्वतंत्रता from Great ब्रिटेन in 1776.
However, by 1804, सब states उत्तर of the Mason और Dixon Line था either abolished गुलामी outright or passed कानून for the क्रमिक abolition of slavery.
In 1787 Congress निषिद्ध गुलामी in the उत्तरपश्चिम Territory.
लकिन slavery gained नई life in the South साथ the कपास उद्योग बाद 1800, and expanded into the Southwest.
The nation थी polarized into slave and free states साथ the Mason-Dixon लकीर, which अलग पेन्सिलवेनिया and Maryland.
The United राज्य और ग्रेट Britain both निषिद्ध the अंतरराष्ट्रीय स्लेव व्यापार in 1808, but the domestic व्यापार, साथ sales to the Deep South, expanded dramatically, and many captives यहूद shipped by the coastwise slave व्यापार.
पहले the 1840s, the दक्षिण was vigorously defending slavery and its expansion into the territories.
In the उत्तर कुछ abolitionists denounced it as गुनाहगार, और numerous anti-slavery शक्तियां अस्वीकृत it as detrimental to the अधिकारों of फ़्री men.
बाद विफल compromises और अब्राहम lincoln 's election, in 1861 eleven स्लेव states broke away to रूप the confederate राज्य of अमेरिका, leading to the अमरीकी सिविल War.
the federal government in 1862 बना abolition of slavery a war लक्ष्य.
In जनवरी 1863 अध्यक्ष lincoln freed स्लेव in the confederacy through the Emancipation उदघोषणा.
बाद the युद्ध, the तेरहवीं amendment, effective दिसम्बर 1865, abolished गुलामी throughout the संपूर्ण United राज्य, सहित the किनारा states और the Indian territories.
इससे the 16th to the 19th सदियां, an अनुमानित 12 लाख africans were shipped as slaves to the americas.
See गुलामी in the americas.
the ग्रेट majority गई to the शुगर बागानों of the वेस्ट Indies or Brazil, where मृत्यु थी high.
परिचय 645,000 were brought to कया is now the United राज्य.
By the 1860 संयुक्त States जनसांख्यिकी, the स्लेव जनसांख्यिकी in the अमरीकी दक्षिण था grown to चार लाख.
of सब 1,515,605 परिवारों in the 15 स्लेव states, nearly 400,000 held slaves ( roughly one in चार ), amounting to 8 % of all अमरीकी families.
जबकि कुछ स्लेव worked as हाउस बन्दों और शहरी artisans, the great majority worked on बागानों or विशाल farms, cultivating lucrative नकदी crops, such as rice, tobacco, शुगर और, बाद 1800, chiefly कपास.
by 1860 most slaves were आयोजित in the गहन दक्षिण, जहाँ they served in work-gangs ; two-thirds worked in कपास.
In small परिचालन, वे worked with उनके स्वामी.
in large plantations वे यहूद निर्देशित by श्वेत paid overseers.
अंतर्गत the प्रणाली कि became chattel slavery ( स्वामित्व of a human being, and of his/her descendants ), a racial element थी आधारभूत : slaves were अश्वेतों of African descent and स्वामित्व, लगभग universally, by whites of यूरोपीय descent.
In the 17th सदी, वर्जिनिया, followed by other दक्षिणी colonies, enacted law that children of slave mothers यहूद born into गुलामी.
स्लेव could लाभ freedom तभी by कार्यशील दूर ( जिससे थी मुश्किल and illegal to do ), or by manumission by owners, जिससे was regulated by राज्य, और became increasingly difficult or निषिद्ध.
in the earliest era of chattel slavery, the colonies also व्यवस्थित work by a प्रणाली of बंधुआ labor known as indentured servitude.
इस typically lasted लिये अनेक सालो लिये both poor europeans और africans alike, to pay बंद the लागत of transport to the colonies.
They contracted for ऐसे arrangements because of ग़रीब economies in उनके घर देशों.
Between 1680 and 1700, as fewer Europeans migrated to the colonies, planters began to आयात अधिक Africans as slaves.
recognizing the महत्व of गुलामी, the हाउस of burgesses in वर्जिनिया enacted a नई slave कोड in 1705 ; it combined a variety of legislation और added नई प्रावधानों enforcing श्वेत सर्वोच्चता in the law.

जाइलम is एक of the दो types of हस्तांतरण ऊतक in vascular पौधे ( फ्लोएम is the अन्य ).
The शब्द xylem is निकला from the यूनानी word ξύλον ( xylon ), meaning `` लकडी '' ; the best-known जाइलम ऊतक is लकडी, हालांकि it is found throughout the संयंत्र.

इस क्लॉक प्रतिनिधित्व shows कुछ of the major units of geological time और definitive कार्यक्रम of धरती history.
The Hadean eon represents the समय पहले चट्टान रिकार्ड of life on Earth ; इसके अपर boundary is now regarded as 4.0 ga ( अरब सालो पहले ).
Other subdivisions प्रतिबिंबित the evolution of जीवन ; the Archean and proterozoic हैं दोनो eons, the Palaeozoic, mesozoic और cenozoic हैं eras of the Phanerozoic eon.
the दो लाख year quaternary काल, the समय of recognizable इंसानो, is too small to be visible at इस scale.
the geologic time स्केल is a प्रणाली of chronological मापन that relates स्तरिकी to time, और is used by geologists, paleontologists, and other धरती scientists to describe the समय और संबंध between कार्यक्रम कि have occurred throughout धरती 's history.
The तालिका of भूगर्भिक समय spans प्रस्तुत यहाँ agrees with the dates और nomenclature set forth by the अंतरराष्ट्रीय आयोग on Stratigraphy standard color कोड of the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Commission on स्तरिकी.
Evidence इससे radiometric dating indicates कि the धरती is about 4.54 billion सालो बूढ़ा.
the भूविज्ञान or deep समय of धरती 's पास्ट has महरूम व्यवस्थित into विभिन्न इकाई according to कार्यक्रम which took प्लेस in प्रत्येक काल.
अलग spans of समय on the gts हैं प्रायः delimited by परिवर्तन in the संयोजन of strata जिससे correspond to उन्हें, indicating major geological or paleontological कार्यक्रम, ऐसे as द्रव्यमान extinctions.

The Harpy त्रिभुज ( Harpia harpyja ) is a neotropical प्रजाति of eagle.
It is sometimes known as the American harpy त्रिभुज to फर्क it इससे the Papuan त्रिभुज जिससे is sometimes known as the नई गिनी Harpy त्रिभुज or Papuan harpy त्रिभुज.
it is the largest और most powerful रैप्टर found in the americas, and among the largest extant प्रजाति of eagles in the संसार.
it प्रायः inhabits tropical lowland rainforests in the अपर ( emergent ) canopy परत.
विनाश of its प्राकृतिक आवास रै seen it vanish इससे many भाग of इसके पूर्व दायरा, and it is nearly extirpated in सेंट्रल America.
Biological classification, or scientific वर्गीकरण in biology, is a method of scientific taxonomy प्रयुक्त to समूह और categorize जीवों into समूह such as genus or species.
These समूह हैं known as taxa ( एकवचन : taxon ).
आधुनिक biological वर्गीकरण has इसके root in the कार्य of carolus लीनियस, जो grouped प्रजाति according to shared शारीरिक विशेषताएँ.
ये groupings have चूंकि been revised to improve consistency with the darwinian principle of common descent.
साथ the introduction of the cladistic method in the late 20th century, phylogenetic taxonomy in जिससे जीवों हैं grouped आधारित purely on inferred evolutionary relatedness, ignoring morphological समानता, रै become आम in some क्षेत्रों of जीवविज्ञान.
Molecular phylogenetics, which uses डीएनए sequences as data, रै also driven many recent revisions and is संभावित to continue doing so.
biological वर्गीकरण belongs to the science of biological systematics.

John Winston ओनो लेनन, ( born John Winston Lennon ; 9 अक्तूबर 1940 – 8 December 1980 ) was an English संगीतकार, सिंगर and songwriter who रोज़ to worldwide कीर्ति as a संस्थापक सदस्य of the Beatles, एक of the सबसे commercially कामयाब और critically acclaimed acts in the इतिहास of लोकप्रिय म्यूज़िक.
साथ Paul mccartney, he formed एक of the most celebrated songwriting partnerships of the 20th सदी.
born और उठाया in लिवरपूल, as a किशोरावस्था लेनन became involved in the skiffle craze ; his पहला band, the Quarrymen, evolved into the Beatles in 1960.
as the समूह disintegrated towards the समाप्त of the दशक, Lennon embarked on a सोलो career that उत्पादित the critically acclaimed एल्बम John lennon/plastic Ono बैंड and Imagine, और iconic गीतों such as `` दे सलाम a मौका `` और `` imagine ``.
After his marriage to Yoko ओनो in 1969, he बदला उसके नाम to जॉन Ono Lennon.
Lennon disengaged खुद इससे the music business in 1975 to devote time to raising उसके infant son शॉन, but re-emerged with ओनो in 1980 साथ the new एल्बम दोगुना काल्पनिक.
He was murdered three सप्ताह after इसके रिलीज.
लेनन revealed a rebellious प्रकृति और acerbic wit in उसके म्यूज़िक, लिखने, drawings, on film और in interviews.
विवादास्पद through his political और सलाम सक्रियता, he स्थानांतरित to नई York नगर in 1971, where उसके criticism of the वियतनाम युद्ध resulted in a lengthy attempt by Richard Nixon 's प्रशासन to deport उसे, जबकि कुछ of his songs were adopted as anthems by the anti-war movement.
as of 2012, लेनन 's solo एल्बम बिक्री in the United States exceed 14 लाख इकाई, and as लेखक, co-writer or performer, he is जिम्मेदार लिये 25 number-one singles on the US Hot 100 चार्ट.
in 2002, a BBC पोल on the 100 महानतम Britons voted उसे आठवीं, and in 2008, रोलिंग स्टोन क्रमित उसे the fifth-greatest सिंगर of सब समय.
He was posthumously inducted into the songwriters हॉल of कीर्ति in 1987 and into the चट्टान और फेंकें हॉल of कीर्ति in 1994.
प्रतिमा of rip वैन Winkle in irvington, नई York, not दूर इससे `` Sunnyside ``, the घर of वॉशिंगटन इरविंग
`` Rip वैन Winkle '' is a छोटी स्टोरी by अमरीकी लेखक वॉशिंगटन Irving published in 1819, as खूब as the name of the स्टोरी 's fictional समर्थक.
Written जबकि Irving was living in Birmingham, इंग्लैण्ड, it was भाग of a collection हकदार The स्केच Book of Geoffrey crayon.
हालांकि the स्टोरी is नियत in New York 's catskill Mountains, Irving बाद admitted, `` जब I wrote the story, i था never महरूम on the catskills. ''
throughout the fifty-five साल इतिहास of the ग्रैमी पुरस्कार, अनेक significant रिकॉर्ड have महरूम नियत.
इस पेज तभी शामिल the competitive पुरस्कार जीती by विभिन्न कलाकारों.
इस करता not शामिल the विभिन्न special awards कि are presented by the नेशनल अकादमी of Recording कला और sciences ऐसे as आजीवन Achievement पुरस्कार, Trustees Awards, तकनीकी पुरस्कार or Legend Awards.
the पेज however does शामिल अन्य non-performance सम्बन्धित Grammys ( ज्ञात as the Craft & उत्पादन फ़ील्ड ) that may have been प्रस्तुत to the artist ( s ).
pee-wee Herman is a comic fictional character निर्मित और portrayed by अमरीकी हास्य पॉल Reubens.
He is बेहतरीन ज्ञात for उसके दो टेलीविज़न series and film श्रेणी दौरान the 1980s.
The childlike pee-wee Herman अक्षर developed as a स्टेज अधिनियम that quickly led to an एचबीओ खास in 1981.
As the stage प्रदर्शन gained further लोकप्रियता, reubens took the character to गति चित्र साथ Pee-wee 's Big एडवेंचर in 1985, toning bas the वयस्क innuendo लिये the अपील of children.
This paved the रास्ता लिये pee-wee 's playhouse, an Emmy पुरस्कार जीतना children 's series that ran on सीबीएस इससे 1986-1991.
another film, बिग Top pee-wee, थी released in 1988.
Due to ऋणात्मक मीडिया ध्यान following a कांड in 1991, reubens decided to shelve his alter ego during the 1990s, and तब धीरे resurrected it दौरान the following decade.
It थी at that समय that reubens addressed योजनाएँ to लिखें a नई Pee-wee film, pee-wee 's Playhouse : The फिल्म.
in जून 2007, reubens appeared as pee-wee herman लिये the first time since 1991 at स्पाइक tv 's यारों ' चुनाव Awards.
कि '70s दिखाएँ is an अमरीकी television काल sitcom that centers on the जीवनदान of a group of teenage मित्रों जीना in the fictional suburban कस्बा of पाइंट प्लेस, विस्कॉन्सिन, इससे may 17, 1976, to December 31, 1979.

Kansas ( ) is a u.S. राज्य located in the Midwestern संयुक्त राज्य.
it is named बाद the Kansas River जिससे flows through it, जिससे in फेरे थी named बाद the Kansa देशी American tribe, जिससे inhabited the क्षेत्रफल.
the जनजाति 's नाम ( natively kką : ze ) is प्रायः कहा to औसत `` people of the हवा '' or `` people of the दक्षिण हवा, '' although इस was probably नहीं the term 's असली अर्थ.
निवासियों of कान्सास हैं पुकारा `` kansans. ''
For thousands of सालो what is now Kansas was घर to numerous and diverse Native अमरीकी जनजातियों.
जनजातियों in the पूर्वी भाग of the राज्य generally जिया in गांवों साथ the river valleys.
जनजातियों in the पश्चिमी part of the राज्य were सेमi- nomadic और hunted large herds of बाइसन.
कान्सास थी first settled by यूरोपीय Americans in the 1830s, but the pace of उपनिवेश त्वरित in the 1850s, in the midst of political युद्धों over the गुलामी समस्या.
When officially opened to उपनिवेश by the u.S. government in 1854, abolitionist free-staters from नई England and pro-slavery settlers इससे neighboring मिसौरी rushed to the territory to determine if Kansas होता become a free राज्य or a स्लेव राज्य.
यूँ, the area थी a hotbed of हिंसा and अराजकता in इसके जल्दी दिनों as ये forces collided, और थी ज्ञात as Bleeding कान्सास.
the abolitionists eventually prevailed और on January 29, 1861, कान्सास entered the संघ as a फ़्री राज्य.
बाद the सिविल War, the जनसांख्यिकी of Kansas grew rapidly, जब waves of आप्रवासियों turned the प्रेयरी into farmland.
आज, कान्सास is one of the सबसे उत्पादक agricultural states, producing high yields of गेहूं, sorghum and sunflowers.
Kansas is the 15th सबसे extensive and the 33rd सबसे populous of the 50 United States.
मनोविज्ञान is an अकादमिक और लागू अनुशासन that involves the वैज्ञानिक पढ़ाई of दिमागी functions और व्यवहार.
मनोविज्ञान has the तात्कालिक goal of understanding individuals और समूह by दोनो establishing सामान्य सिद्धान्त और researching विशिष्ट cases, and by अनेक accounts it ultimately aims to लाभ समाज.
in this फ़ील्ड, a professional or researcher is पुकारा a मनोवैज्ञानिक और can be वर्गीकृत as a सोशल, behavioral, or cognitive वैज्ञानिक.
psychologists attempt to समझे the भूमिका of दिमागी functions in व्यक्तिगत और सोशल बर्ताव, जबकि also exploring the physiological and neurobiological प्रक्रियाओं कि underlie certain संज्ञानात्मक कृत्यों and व्यवहार.
Psychologists explore अवधारणाओं such as बोध, cognition, ध्यान, जज्बात, phenomenology, प्रेरणा, brain functioning, व्यक्तित्व, behavior, और interpersonal relationships.
psychologists of विविध धारियाँ also consider the unconscious दिमाग.
Psychologists employ empirical विधि to infer causal and correlational relationships between psychosocial variables.
In addition, or in विपक्ष, to employing अनुभवजन्य and deductive विधि, some—especially नैदानिक और counseling psychologists—at times rely upon symbolic निर्वचन and अन्य आगमनात्मक तकनीकों.
मनोविज्ञान has महरूम described as a `` हब विज्ञान '', साथ मनोवैज्ञानिक निष्कर्षों linking to शोध and perspectives from the सोशल sciences, प्राकृतिक sciences, आयुर्विज्ञान, and the मानवता, such as दर्शनशास्त्र.
जबकि psychological ज्ञान is often लागू to the मूल्यांकन और उपचार of दिमागी health problems, it is भी directed towards समझना and solving problems in many different spheres of इंसान activity.
the बहुमत of psychologists हैं शामिल in कुछ दयालु of therapeutic role, practicing in नैदानिक, counseling, or school जमावट.
Many do वैज्ञानिक शोध on a wide दायरा of विषय सम्बन्धित to दिमागी processes and बर्ताव, और typically कार्य in विश्वविद्यालयों मनोविज्ञान departments or teach in other अकादमिक जमावट ( e.g., medical schools, hospitals ).
कुछ हैं employed in औद्योगिक और organizational जमावट, or in अन्य क्षेत्रों ऐसे as human विकास and aging, sports, health, और the media, as खूब as in forensic छानबीन और other पहलुओं of विधि.
थामस Jefferson ( अप्रैल 13, 1743 ( अप्रैल 2, 1743 o.S. ) – जुलाई 4, 1826 ) थी an अमरीकी founding Father, the प्रिंसिपल लेखक of the घोषणा of Independence ( 1776 ) और the तीसरा अध्यक्ष of the United States ( 1801–1809 ).
at the शुरूआत of the अमरीकी क्रान्ति, he served in the Continental कॉंग्रेस, representing वर्जिनिया and then परोसा as a wartime Governor of वर्जिनिया ( 1779–1781 ).
Just बाद the war ended, from mid-1784 Jefferson परोसा as a diplomat, stationed in पेरिस.
in May 1785, he became the United राज्य मंत्री to फ़्रांस.
जेफरसन थी the पहला संयुक्त राज्य Secretary of राज्य ( 1790–1793 ) serving under अध्यक्ष जार्ज Washington.
साथ उसके close dost जेम्स मैडिसन he organized the democratic-republican पार्टी, and subsequently resigned from वॉशिंगटन 's cabinet.
निर्वाचित Vice अध्यक्ष in 1796, जब he आए in second to John एडम्स of the Federalists, जेफरसन opposed एडम्स और with मैडिसन secretly लिखा the Kentucky और वर्जिनिया रिज़ॉल्यूशन, जिससे attempted to nullify the एलियन और राजद्रोह अधिनियमों.
निर्वाचित president in कया जेफरसन called the क्रान्ति of 1800, he oversaw the खरीदें of the विशाल louisiana territory from फ़्रांस ( 1803 ), and sent the लुईस and क्लार्क Expedition ( 1804–1806 ) to explore the नई west.
उसके दूसरी पद थी घिरा with troubles at home, ऐसे as the विफल treason विचारण of his पूर्व वाइस अध्यक्ष आरोन burr.
साथ escalating ट्रबल साथ ब्रिटेन जो थी चुनौतीपूर्ण American neutrality और threatening शिपिंग at समुद्र, he tried आर्थिक warfare साथ his embargo कानून which only क्षतिग्रस्त American व्यापार.
In 1803, अध्यक्ष Jefferson initiated a प्रक्रम of Indian tribal हटाना और relocation to the louisiana Territory west of the Mississippi नदी, in order to खोलें lands लिये eventual American settlers.
a नेता in the आत्मज्ञान, जेफरसन थी a polymath who spoke पाँच भाषाएं धड़ल्ले और was deeply interested in विज्ञान, आविष्कार, architecture, धर्म और दर्शनशास्त्र, interests that led him to the founding of the विश्वविद्यालयों of वर्जिनिया बाद उसके presidency.
he designed उसके अपना विशाल mansion on a 5,000 एकड़ plantation near Charlottesville, वर्जिनिया, which he named Monticello.
जबकि not a notable orator, जेफरसन थी a skilled writer and corresponded साथ अनेक influential लोगों in अमेरिका और यूरोपीय throughout उसके वयस्क जीवन.
Though जेफरसन owned many स्लेव, he opposed the संस्था all his जीवन and नतीजतन treated and took care of उन्हें बहुत खूब and expected उन्हें to कार्य no अधिक than फ़्री farmers.
चूंकि 1802 इतिहासकारों और अन्य have been divided over the विवाद of whether जेफरसन थी the पिता of एक or अधिक children belonging to सैली Hemings, a slave at Monticello. ''
इतिहासकारों are भी in disagreement साथ how much Jefferson was committed to the anti-slavery कारण.
In 1807, अध्यक्ष जेफरसन हस्ताक्षरित into law a bill that banned the importation of स्लेव into the संयुक्त राज्य.
बाद मार्था जेफरसन, his बीवी of ग्यारह years, died in 1782, जेफरसन remained a widower for the rest of उसके life ; उनके विवाह उत्पादित छह children, of जिसको दो survived to adulthood.
हालांकि जेफरसन रै been criticized by अनेक आधुनिक दिन विद्वानों over the समस्या of slavery, he remains रेटेड as one of the greatest u.S. राष्ट्रपतियों.
`` Sun नगर '' is a 1985 विरोध song लिखा by स्टीवन Van zandt, produced by Van Zandt और Arthur बेकर and recorded by Artists संयुक्त विरूद्ध Apartheid to convey विपक्ष to the दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी policy of apartheid.
the primary अर्थात् of that विपक्ष is to declare कि सब the artists शामिल would इंकार कोई और सब offers to perform at Sun नगर, a रिज़ॉर्ट which was स्तिथ in bantustan of Bophuthatswana, एक of a number of internationally अपरिचित supposed `` independent '' states निर्मित by the South अफ़्रीकी government to forcibly relocate its black जनसांख्यिकी.

the नेशनल बास्केट संघ ( एनबीए ) is a major professional बास्केट लीग in उत्तर America.
it थी संस्थापित in 1946 as the Basketball Association of America ( BAA ).
the लीग adopted its current नाम at the प्रारंभ of the जब it मिलाया साथ the National बास्केट लीग ( NBL ).
the एनबीए Finals is the चैंपियनशिप series for the NBA और the निष्कर्ष of the sport 's postseason.
The जीतना team of the series receives the Larry O'Brien चैंपियनशिप Trophy.
Players इससे the जीतना team प्रायः receive चैंपियनशिप rings from the टोली honoring उनके योगदान.

the क्रमांक of championships won by NBA सुपरस्टार is प्रायः प्रयुक्त as a मापन of उनके विशालता.
बोस्टन Celtics center विधेयक Russell holds the record लिये the सबसे एनबीए championships जीती with 11 शीर्षक दौरान his 13-year playing करियर.
he जीती his first championship with the Boston सेल्टिक्स in his rookie साल.
afterwards, he गई on to win 10 championships in the अगला 12 सालो, including आठ consecutive championships इससे 1959 to 1966.
He won the पिछला दो championships in 1968 और 1969 as player-coach.
Russell 's teammate, sam Jones, जीती 10 championships इससे 1959 to 1969, the दूसरी सबसे in NBA इतिहास.
Four सेल्टिक्स players, tom Heinsohn, K. C. जोन्स, Satch सैंडर्स और John Havlicek, जीती eight championships प्रत्येक.
दो अन्य Celtics, जिम Loscutoff और Frank Ramsey, won seven championships प्रत्येक.
Four players, Bob Cousy, Kareem Abdul-Jabbar, माइकल जॉर्डन and scottie pippen, won six championships प्रत्येक.
Jordan और pippen हैं सदस्यों of the शिकागो Bulls team जो जीती तीन लगातार championships twice in the 1990s.
रॉबर्ट horry और जॉन salley are the only players to have जीती the championships with तीन अलग टीमों.
