सटीकता indicates निकटता of measurement परिणाम to the true value, precision to the repeatability, or reproducibility of the मापन
in the फ़ील्ड of विज्ञान, अभियान्त्रिकी, industry, और statistics, the accuracy of a मापन प्रणाली is the degree of closeness of measurements of a quantity to that quantity 's वास्तविक ( true ) मान.
The precision of a measurement प्रणाली, भी called reproducibility or repeatability, is the उपाधि to जिससे repeated माप अंतर्गत unchanged conditions दिखाएँ the same results.
हालांकि the दो शब्द reproducibility and repeatability can be synonymous in colloquial उपयोग, they हैं deliberately contrasted in the context of the वैज्ञानिक method.
a measurement प्रणाली can be सटीक but नहीं precise, precise लकिन नहीं सटीक, neither, or दोनो.
For उदाहरण, if an experiment contains a व्यवस्थित error, तब increasing the नमूना आकार generally increases परिशुद्धता but does नहीं improve सटीकता.
The परिणाम would be a consistent yet inaccurate स्ट्रिंग of results इससे the flawed प्रयोग.
Eliminating the व्यवस्थित गलती improves सटीकता लकिन करता not बदलें परिशुद्धता.
a मापन system is designated valid if it is both सटीक और precise.
Related terms शामिल पूर्वाग्रह ( non- यादृच्छिक or निर्देशित प्रभाव caused by a factor or factors unrelated to the independent परिवर्तनीय ) और गलती ( यादृच्छिक variability ).
the terminology is भी applied to अप्रत्यक्ष measurements—that is, values obtained by a computational कार्यविधि इससे observed data.
in जोड to accuracy और precision, measurements may भी have a मापन resolution, which is the smallest बदलें in the underlying physical मात्रा कि produces a जवाब in the measurement.
In the case of पूरा reproducibility, ऐसे as जब rounding a क्रमांक to a representable फ्लोटिंग पाइंट number, the शब्द precision रै a meaning नहीं सम्बन्धित to reproducibility.
लिये उदाहरण, in the आईईईई 754-2008 मानक it अर्थात् the क्रमांक of bits in the significand, so it is used as a माप for the सापेक्ष सटीकता साथ जिससे an arbitrary क्रमांक can be represented.
बकवास in इसके literal meaning refers to the अधिनियम of sexual मैथुन.
it is an अंग्रेज़ी word कि is प्रायः प्रयुक्त as a profanity, either to denote तिरस्कार or as an intensifier.
the उत्पत्ति of the शब्द is अस्पष्ट.
It is usually माना to be पहला attested to around 1475, लकिन it may be considerably पुरानी.
In आधुनिक usage, fuck और its डेरिवेटिव ( ऐसे as कमीने और fucking ) can be प्रयुक्त in the स्थिति of a noun, a क्रिया, an क्रियाशील or an adverb.

एनिमेटेड, color-coded मैप showing the विभिन्न महाद्वीपों और regions.
Depending on the सम्मेलन and मॉडल, some continents may be संचित or subdivided : लिये उदाहरण, यूरेशिया is सबसे प्रायः subdivided into यूरोपीय and Asia ( red shades ), जबकि उत्तर and दक्षिण अमेरिका are sometimes recognized as एक अमरीकी continent ( ग्रीन shades ).

जातियाँ property is a वैवाहिक property शासन कि originated in सिविल विधि jurisdictions और is now also मिला in कुछ आम law jurisdictions.
the राज्य of the संयुक्त States that recognize जातियाँ property are primarily in the वेस्ट ; it थी inherited इससे मैक्सिको 's ganancial जातियाँ प्रणाली, जिससे itself थी inherited from स्पेनी विधि ( a Roman -derived सिविल विधि प्रणाली ) and ultimately from the visigoths.
जबकि under स्पेनी नियम louisiana अपनाया the ganancial जातियाँ system of acquests और gains, जिससे replaced the परंपरागत French community of movables और acquests in इसके civil विधि system.
मैप of the संयुक्त States साथ community property राज्य highlighted in red.
in addition to the highlighted राज्य, Alaska is a separate प्रॉपर्टी राज्य कि permits युगल to ऑप्ट into a जातियाँ प्रॉपर्टी व्यवस्था.
in a जातियाँ प्रॉपर्टी क्षेत्राधिकार, सबसे प्रॉपर्टी acquired during the विवाह ( except for उपहार or inheritances ) —the जातियाँ, or communio bonorum—is स्वामित्व jointly by दोनो spouses और is divided upon तलाक, annulment or death.
संयुक्त स्वामित्व is automatically presumed by law in the अनुपस्थिति of specific evidence कि would पाइंट to a contrary conclusion for a particular टुकड़ा of property.
प्रभाग of जातियाँ property may take प्लेस by item, by splitting सब वस्तुएं or by मान.
in कुछ jurisdictions, ऐसे as California, a 50/50 प्रभाग of जातियाँ प्रॉपर्टी is strictly mandated by statute, अर्थ कि the फ़ोकस तब शिफ्ट to whether particular वस्तुएं हैं to be वर्गीकृत as जातियाँ or separate प्रॉपर्टी.
in other jurisdictions, ऐसे as टेक्सास, a divorce अदालत may डिक्री an `` equitable वितरण `` of जातियाँ property, which may result in an गैरबराबरी प्रभाग of ऐसे.
in non-community property states property may be divided by equitable वितरण.
generally speaking, the प्रॉपर्टी that each संगी brings into the marriage or receives by gift, bequest or devise दौरान विवाह is पुकारा पृथक प्रॉपर्टी ( i.e., नहीं community प्रॉपर्टी ).
देखिए division of property.
प्रभाग of community debts may नहीं be the same as प्रभाग of community प्रॉपर्टी.
For उदाहरण, in कैलिफ़ोर्निया, community property is required to be divided `` equally '' while community debt is जरूरी to be divided `` equitably ''.
Property that is स्वामित्व by एक spouse before the marriage is the पृथक property of that spouse, जबतक the property is `` transmuted '' into community प्रॉपर्टी.

a हाथ ( med. / lat. : manus, pl. manūs ) is a prehensile, multi- fingered extremity स्तिथ at the end of an भुजा or forelimb of primates और इंसानो, chimpanzees, बंदरों, और lemurs.
a few अन्य vertebrates ऐसे as the कोआला ( जिससे has two opposable thumbs on प्रत्येक `` हाथ '' और fingerprints remarkably समान to इंसान फिंगरप्रिंट ) are प्रायः वर्णित as having either `` hands '' or `` paws '' on their सामने limbs.
हैंड्स हैं the प्रमुख structures for physically manipulating the पर्यावरण, used लिये both gross मोटर कौशल ( ऐसे as grasping a large ऑब्जेक्ट ) and ठीक मोटर कौशल ( such as picking up a small कंकड़ ).
the उंगलियों contain कुछ of the densest क्षेत्रों of तंत्रिका endings on the देह, हैं the richest source of tactile प्रतिक्रिया, and have the महानतम positioning capability of the body ; यूँ the sense of टच is intimately associated with hands.
जैसे अन्य paired अंगों ( आँखें, feet, legs ), प्रत्येक hand is dominantly नियंत्रित by the opposing brain hemisphere, so that handedness, or the preferred हाथ choice for single-handed activities ऐसे as writing साथ a pencil, reflects व्यक्तिगत brain कामकाज.
कुछ विकासवादी anatomists use the पद hand to refer to the appendage of अंक on the forelimb more generally — for उदाहरण, in the context of whether the तीन अंक of the बर्ड हाथ शामिल the same homologous loss of two अंक as in the dinosaur हाथ.
the human hand रै 27 हड्डियों, not सहित the sesamoid bones जिससे क्रमांक varies between लोगों.

Digital घड़ियाँ are often संबद्ध साथ इलेक्ट्रॉनिक ड्राइव, लकिन the `` digital '' description refers तभी to the प्रदर्शक, not to the ड्राइव यांत्रिकी.

The history of the फलक game Monopoly can be traced back to the जल्दी 20th सदी.
The earliest ज्ञात design थी by the अमरीकी, Elizabeth magie, patented in 1904 लकिन मौजूदा as early as 1902.
magie 's original intent थी to प्रकाशित a board game to illustrate an आर्थिक principle, namely the georgist concept of a सिंगल जमीन मान कर.
A श्रेणी of फलक games were developed from 1906 through the 1930s कि शामिल the buying and selling of जमीन and the development of कि land.
By 1934, a फलक game था महरूम निर्मित much जैसे the संस्करण of एकाधिकार बेची by पार्कर Brothers and इसके सम्बन्धित कंपनियाँ through the rest of the 20th century, और into the 21st.
Several लोगों, ज़्यादातर in the midwestern संयुक्त States और near the East Coast, contributed to the खेल 's design and evolution.
by the 1970s, the विचार कि the खेल had been created solely by Charles darrow था become popular folklore ; it थी printed in the game 's निर्देश लिये अनेक years, in a 1974 किताब devoted to एकाधिकार, and was cited in a सामान्य किताब परिचय खिलौने even as recently as 2007.
भी a मार्गदर्शिका to family games प्रकाशित लिये रीडर 's डाइजेस्ट in 2003 तभी gave क्रेडिट to darrow and Elizabeth magie, erroneously stating that Magie 's असली game थी निर्मित in the 1800s, और not acknowledging कोई of the खेल 's विकास between Magie 's creation of the खेल, and the eventual publication by Parker भाइयो.
भी in the 1970s, Professor Ralph anspach, who था himself प्रकाशित a फलक game intended to illustrate the सिद्धान्त of दोनो monopolies and trust busting, fought Parker भाइयो और इसके then parent कम्पनी, सामान्य मिलों, over the trademarks of the एकाधिकार फलक game.
through the शोध of anspach और अन्य, much of the जल्दी इतिहास of the game थी `` rediscovered ''.
Anspach confronted Maxine ब्रैडी, लेखक of the 1974 किताब the एकाधिकार Book : Strategy and Tactics of the संसार 's सबसे लोकप्रिय खेल over the actual इतिहास of the खेल on Barry farber 's नई यॉर्क नगर talk show in 1975.
क्युकी of the lengthy अदालत process, including appeals, the legal status of पार्कर Brothers ' trademarks on the game was नहीं settled जबतक 1985.
the खेल 's name remains a पंजीकृत ट्रेडमार्क of पार्कर Brothers, as do its विशिष्ट design elements.
At the निष्कर्ष of the court मामला, the खेल 's लोगो and ग्राफिक डिज़ाइन तत्व became part of a larger एकाधिकार ब्रांड, licensed by पार्कर Brothers ' जनक कंपनियाँ onto a variety of items through the उपस्थित दिन.

in baseball, a sacrifice fly is a batted बॉल कि satisfies चार criteria:
There हैं fewer than दो outs जब the ball is hit.
The बॉल is hit to the आउटफील्ड ( मेला or बेईमानी ), or to infield बेईमानी territory.
The बैटर is put आउट because an outfielder ( or an infielder running in the outfield, or foul territory ) catches the बॉल on the fly ( alternatively if the batter होता have been out if नहीं for an गलती or if the outfielder drops the बॉल और another धावक is put आउट ).
a धावक जो is already on आधार स्कोर on the play.

Minnesota ( ) is a U.S. state स्तिथ in the Midwestern संयुक्त राज्य.
मिनेसोटा was carved आउट of the पूर्वी half of the मिनेसोटा territory और admitted to the संघ as the 32nd राज्य on May 11, 1858.

Minnesota is known for its अपेक्षाकृत mixed सोशल और political orientations, और रै a ऊँची रेट of नागरिक participation और वोटर turnout.
मिनेसोटा ranks among the healthiest राज्य, और रै a highly साक्षर population.

Grants हैं non-repayable निधि by एक पार्टी ( ग्रान्ट makers ), often a government विभाग, निगम, foundation or trust, to a, प्रायः ( but not सदा ) a nonprofit एंटिटी, educational institution, कारोबार or an individual.
In order to प्राप्त a grant, कुछ रूप of `` ग्रान्ट Writing '' प्रायः referred to as either a प्रस्ताव or an application is usually जरूरी.
Most अनुदान are made to fund a specific प्रोजेक्ट and require कुछ स्तर of compliance और रिपोर्टिंग.
the ग्रान्ट writing process involves an आवेदक submitting a proposal ( or submission ) to a potential funder, either on the आवेदक 's own पहल or in जवाब to a Request लिये प्रस्ताव इससे the funder.
Other अनुदान can be दिए to individuals, ऐसे as पीड़ितों of प्राकृतिक disasters or individuals who seek to open a छोटी business.
Sometimes grant makers आवश्यकता ग्रान्ट seekers to have some रूप of tax-exempt औकात, be a registered nonprofit संगठन or a लोकल government.
For उदाहरण, tiered funding for a फ्रीवे हैं बहुत large grants negotiated at government नीति स्तर.
however छोटी grants may be provided by a government एजेंसी ( e.g. municipal सरकारी ).
project-related funding involving सरकारें, कारोबार, समुदायों, and individuals is often arranged by application either in लिखने or ऑनलाइन.
Naturally occurring कोबाल्ट ( co ) is composed of 1 stable isotope, 59co. 28 radioisotopes have महरूम characterized with the सबसे stable being 60Co साथ a half-life of 5.2714 years, 57Co साथ a half-life of 271.79 दिनों, 56co with a half-life of 77.27 days, और 58co with a half-life of 70.86 दिनों.

This तत्व also रै 11 मेटा states, सब of जिससे have half-lives less than 15 minutes.
The isotopes of कोबाल्ट range in atomic वज़न from 47co to 75Co.

निकिता sergeyevich khrushchev ( – सितंबर 11, 1971 ) led the सोवियत Union during भाग of the ठंडा युद्ध.
he परोसा as पहला सचिव of the Communist पार्टी of the सोवियत Union इससे 1953 to 1964, और as अध्यक्ष of the Council of मंत्रियों, or प्रीमियर, इससे 1958 to 1964.
Khrushchev was responsible लिये the partial de-stalinization of the Soviet संघ, लिये बैकिंग the प्रगति of the जल्दी Soviet space कार्यक्रम, and लिये several relatively उदार reforms in areas of घरेलू नीति.
khrushchev 's party colleagues removed उसे इससे शक्ति in 1964, replacing उसे साथ लियोनिद Brezhnev as पहला सचिव and Alexei Kosygin as प्रीमियर.
khrushchev थी born in the रूसी गाँव of kalinovka in 1894, बंद to the present-day किनारा between Russia और Ukraine.
He थी employed as a metalworker in उसके youth, और during the रूसी सिविल युद्ध थी a राजनैतिक commissar.
साथ the सहायता of lazar Kaganovich, he worked उसके रास्ता up the सोवियत पदानुक्रम.
he समर्थित जोसेफ Stalin 's purges, और approved thousands of रखवाले.
in 1939, स्टालिन भेजा उसे to govern Ukraine, and he जारी the purges there.
During what was known in the Soviet Union as the Great Patriotic युद्ध ( Eastern Front of संसार War ii ), khrushchev थी again a commissar, serving as an intermediary between स्टालिन और his generals.
Khrushchev थी present at the खूनी रक्षा of stalingrad, a fact he took ग्रेट अभिमान in throughout उसके life.
बाद the युद्ध, he returned to युक्त पहले होने recalled to Moscow as एक of स्टालिन 's close advisers.
in the शक्ति struggle triggered by स्टालिन 's मौत in 1953, khrushchev, बाद अनेक सालो, उभरा विजयी.
on February 25, 1956, at the 20th पार्टी Congress, he delivered the `` Secret Speech, '' denouncing स्टालिन 's purges and ushering in a कम repressive era in the सोवियत संघ.
उसके domestic policies, aimed at bettering the lives of ordinary नागरिकों, यहूद often अप्रभावी, विशेषकर in the क्षेत्रफल of कृषि.
Hoping आखिरकार to rely on missiles लिये national defense, khrushchev ordered major कटौती in conventional शक्तियां.
Despite the कटौती, khrushchev 's नियम देखी the tensest सालो of the Cold War, culminating in the Cuban मिसाइल Crisis.
Some of khrushchev 's नीतियों were देखी as erratic, विशेषकर by उसके उभरते विरोधियों, जो quietly rose in शक्ति और अपदस्थ उसे in अक्तूबर 1964.
he किया नहीं suffer the घातक fate of some previous losers of सोवियत शक्ति struggles, लकिन थी pensioned off साथ an apartment in मास्को and a dacha in the countryside.
उसके lengthy memoirs यहूद smuggled to the वेस्ट और प्रकाशित in भाग in 1970.
khrushchev died in 1971 of heart बीमारी.
अपर जठरांत्र ( gi ) bleeding refers to hemorrhage in the अपर जठरांत्र ट्रैक्ट.
the anatomic cut-off लिये अपर GI bleeding is the ligament of treitz, जिससे connects the चौथी portion of the duodenum to the diaphragm near the splenic flexure of the कोलन.
अपर GI bleeds are considered medical emergencies, and आवश्यकता admission to हॉस्पिटल लिये urgent diagnosis और प्रबन्धन.
due to अग्रिम in medications और endoscopy, अपर gi hemorrhage is now usually treated without सर्जरी.
संसार जनसांख्यिकी estimates from 1800 to 2100, based on un 2010 projections ( रेड, नारंगी, green ) and us Census ब्यूरो ऐतिहासिक estimates ( black ).
Actual अंकित जनसांख्यिकी आंकड़े हैं in blue.
according to the highest अनुमान, the world population may rise to 16 अरब by 2100 ; according to the न्यूनतम estimate, it may decline to 6 billion.
The संसार जनसांख्यिकी is the कुल क्रमांक of living humans on Earth.
as of आज, it is estimated to क्रमांक अरब by the United राज्य Census ब्यूरो ( USCB ).
the uscb estimates कि the संसार population exceeded 7 अरब on March 12, 2012.
According to a पृथक estimate by the संयुक्त Nations जनसांख्यिकी निधि, it पहुँचे इस पड़ाव on अक्तूबर 31, 2011.
the संसार population रै अनुभवी निरन्तर growth since the end of the Great अकाल and the ब्लैक मौत in 1350, when it stood at around 370 लाख.
The highest दरों of विकास – वैश्विक population increases above 1.8 % प्रति year – यहूद देखी briefly दौरान the 1950s, और लिये a longer period during the 1960s and 1970s.
The विकास rate peaked at 2.2 % in 1963, और था अस्वीकृत to 1.1 % by 2011.
कुल annual births यहूद highest in the लेट 1980s at परिचय 138 लाख, और are अभी expected to remain essentially निरंतर at उनके 2011 level of 134 लाख, जबकि deaths क्रमांक 56 लाख per साल, और हैं expected to बढ़ाएँ to 80 लाख प्रति year by 2040.
Current projections दिखाएँ a जारी increase in जनसांख्यिकी in the निकट भविष्य ( लकिन a स्थिर मनाही in the जनसांख्यिकी growth rate ), साथ the वैश्विक जनसांख्यिकी expected to reach between 7.5 and 10.5 billion by 2050.
विभिन्न longer-term estimates भविष्यवाणी further विकास, stagnation, or भी overall मनाही in the global जनसांख्यिकी by 2150.
कुछ विश्लेषकों have questioned the स्थिरता of further संसार population growth, citing the growing pressures on the environment, वैश्विक food आपूर्तियाँ, और उर्जा संसाधन.

knuckle mnemonic for the क्रमांक of days in प्रत्येक माह of the Gregorian पंचांग.
प्रत्येक projecting knuckle represents a 31-day माह.
A mnemonic (, साथ a मूक `` m '' ), or mnemonic device, is कोई सीखना तकनीक कि aids सूचना retention.
mnemonics उद्देश्य to अनुवाद सूचना into a रूप कि the इंसान brain can retain better than इसके असली form.
भी the प्रक्रम of applying इस परिवर्तन might already सहायता the ट्रांसफ़र of सूचना to long-term memory.
Commonly encountered mnemonics हैं प्रायः for lists और in auditory form, such as short poems, acronyms, or यादगार phrases, लकिन mnemonics can भी be for other types of सूचना and in विज़ुअल or kinesthetic forms.
उनके उपयोग is आधारित on the observation कि the human mind more easily remembers spatial, personal, surprising, शारीरिक, यौन, humorous, or वरना 'relatable ' information, rather than more abstract or impersonal फ़ॉर्म of information.
the word mnemonic is derived इससे the प्राचीन Greek word μνημονικός ( mnēmonikos ), अर्थ `` of मेमोरी '' and is सम्बन्धित to mnemosyne ( `` remembrance '' ), the नाम of the देवी of memory in Greek mythology.
दोनो of ये शब्द are derived from μνήμη ( mnēmē ), `` स्मरण, मेमोरी ''.
Mnemonics in antiquity were सबसे often considered in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of कया is today ज्ञात as the Art of memory.
प्राचीन यूनानियों और romans विशिष्ट between दो प्रकार of मेमोरी : the 'natural ' memory और the 'artificial ' memory.
the पूर्व is inborn, और is the एक that everyone uses automatically और without सोच.
The कृत्रिम memory in कंट्रास्ट रै to be trained और विकसित through the learning and practicing of a किस्में of mnemonic तकनीकों.
mnemonic प्रणालियों are special तकनीकों or strategies consciously प्रयुक्त to improve मेमोरी, it helps employ सूचना already भंडारित in long-term मेमोरी to मेक memorization an easier task.
President Bush हस्ताक्षर the No चाइल्ड बाएँ पीछे Act at हैमिल्टन h.s. in हैमिल्टन, Ohio.
the No चाइल्ड Left पीछे अधिनियम of 2001 ( nclb ) is a संयुक्त राज्य अधिनियम of Congress कि is a reauthorization of the elementary and द्वितीयक Education Act, जिससे included Title i, the सरकारी 's फ्लैगशिप aid कार्यक्रम for disadvantaged विद्यार्थी.
NCLB supports standards-based शिक्षा सुधार आधारित on the premise कि सेटिंग ऊँची मानकों और establishing measurable लक्ष्य can improve individual outcomes in education.
the Act requires राज्य to develop आकलन in मौलिक कौशल.
राज्य must give ये आकलन to all विद्यार्थी at चुनें ग्रेड स्तर in अनुक्रम to receive संघीय school funding.
the Act करता नहीं assert a national achievement मानक ; मानकों are नियत by each individual राज्य.
NCLB विस्तारित the federal role in पब्लिक शिक्षा through सालाना testing, सालाना academic प्रगति, report cards, टीचर योग्यता, और funding परिवर्तन.
the विधेयक passed in the u.S. कॉंग्रेस साथ bipartisan support.

A pickup ट्रक or pick-up, प्रायः बस referred to as a pickup, is a लाइट मोटर vehicle साथ an open-top, पश्च कार्गो क्षेत्रफल ( bed ).
In North अमेरिका, the पद पिकअप is used for light ट्रक with a हल्का duty chassis और फैक्टरी निर्मित, integrated bed, as well as for coupé यूटिलिटी वाहनों, प्रायः आधारित on a personal car chassis, but भी प्रायः on a special dedicated chassi लिये such उपयोग.
कुछ देशों have उनके own terms समान to pickup, such as ute in ऑस्ट्रेलिया और नई Zealand, or bakkie in South अफ़्रीकी.
Large पिकअप trucks हैं somewhat विरल in यूरोपीय, जहाँ वैन और लाइट lorries हैं commonly प्रयुक्त लिये similar भूमिकाएँ.
इस 15th-century depiction of Charlemagne and Pope Adrian I shows a well-bred medieval horse साथ मेहराबदार गर्दन, परिष्कृत head और सुरुचिपूर्ण gait.
Horses in the Middle Ages differed in आकार, build and नस्ल from the आधुनिक घोड़ा, और were, on average, smaller.
वे यहूद भी अधिक सेंट्रल to society than उनके modern counterparts, being essential for war, कृषि, and हस्तांतरण.
नतीजतन, विशिष्ट प्रकार of घोड़ा developed, अनेक of which have no modern equivalent.
जबकि an understanding of modern घोड़ा breeds and equestrianism is vital लिये कोई analysis of the मध्यकालीन घोड़ा, शोधकर्ताओं also need to consider documentary ( दोनो written और सचित्र ) and पुरातत्व प्रमाण.
Horses in the मध्य आयु were rarely differentiated by नस्ल, लकिन rather by उपयोग.
This led उन्हें to be described, लिये उदाहरण, as `` chargers `` ( युद्ध घोड़े ), `` palfreys `` ( सवारी घोड़े ), cart घोड़े or packhorses.
सन्दर्भ is भी given to उनके place of उत्पत्ति, such as `` Spanish घोड़े, '' लकिन whether इस referred to एक breed or several is अनजान.
another परेशानी arising during कोई study of मध्यकालीन दस्तावेज़ or साहित्य is the लचीलापन of the medieval languages, जहाँ अनेक शब्द can be प्रयुक्त लिये one thing ( or, conversely, अनेक objects are referred to by one word ).
Words ऐसे as ' courser ' और 'charger ' हैं used interchangeably ( भी भीतर एक document ), and जहाँ one epic may speak disparagingly of a rouncey, another praises इसके कौशल and swiftness.
Significant technological अग्रिम in equestrian उपकरण, प्रायः introduced इससे अन्य संस्कृतियों, allowed for significant परिवर्तन in both warfare और कृषि.
In particular, improved डिजाइन for the solid-treed काठी as well as the आगमन of the रकाब, नाल और घोड़ा कॉलर यहूद significant अग्रिम in मध्यकालीन society.
नतीजतन, the assumptions और theories विकसित by इतिहासकारों are not definitive, and बहस स्टिल rages on अनेक मुद्दे, ऐसे as the प्रजनन or आकार of the horse, और a क्रमांक of sources जरूर be consulted in अनुक्रम to समझे the breadth of the subject.

A desert is a landscape or प्रदेश of जमीन कि is बहुत शुष्क because of कम वर्षा amounts ( precipitation ), often has little कवरेज by पौधे, और in जिससे streams dry up unless they are supplied by water from बाहर क्षेत्रों.
रेगिस्तान can also be वर्णित as क्षेत्रों where अधिक जल is खोया by evapotranspiration than जलप्रपात as precipitation.
मरुस्थल पौधे जरूर have special adaptations to जीवित with इस little जल.
रेगिस्तान generally प्राप्त कम than 25 cm of बरसात ( वर्षण ) प्रत्येक year.
Semideserts or steppes हैं regions which प्राप्त between and.
in the köppen जलवायु वर्गीकरण प्रणाली, रेगिस्तान are classed as bwh ( hot मरुस्थल ) or BWk ( शीतोष्ण मरुस्थल ).
in the thornthwaite climate classification प्रणाली, रेगिस्तान would be classified as arid megathermal climates.
World War i ( wwi ) थी a global war केंद्रित in यूरोपीय कि began on 28 जुलाई 1914 और lasted जबतक 11 नवम्बर 1918.
It was predominantly called the संसार युद्ध or the ग्रेट युद्ध from its occurrence until the प्रारंभ of संसार War ii in 1939, and the First संसार युद्ध or संसार युद्ध I thereafter.
It involved सब the संसार 's great शक्तियां, जिससे were समवेत in दो opposing alliances : the allies ( आधारित on the Triple Entente of the United Kingdom, फ़्रांस और रूस ) and the सेंट्रल शक्तियां ( originally the ट्रिपल Alliance of जर्मनी, austria-hungary और Italy ; but, as austria–hungary had taken the अप्रिय विरूद्ध the अनुबंध, Italy did not डालें into the युद्ध ).
ये alliances यहूद दोनो reorganised और विस्तारित as more nations entered the war : Italy, Japan and the United States joined the allies, and the उस्मानी Empire और बुल्गारिया the सेंट्रल Powers.
ultimately, अधिक than 70 million सैन्य कर्मियों, सहित 60 लाख europeans, were mobilised in one of the largest युद्धों in history.
अधिक than 9 लाख combatants were मारे, largely because of technological advancements कि led to enormous increases in the lethality of हथियार बगैर सम्बन्धित सुधार in protection or mobility.
it was the fifth- deadliest विरोध in संसार इतिहास, subsequently paving the way लिये विभिन्न political परिवर्तन, ऐसे as revolutions in many of the राष्ट्र involved.
One of the long-term कल्याणकारी of the युद्ध was the पुनरुत्थान of imperialism in the विदेशी नीतियों of the ग्रेट शक्तियां of यूरोपीय.
More तत्काल, the assassination of archduke Franz Ferdinand of Austria, the वारिस to the सिंहासन of austria-hungary, on 28 जून 1914 by यूगोस्लाव nationalist gavrilo Princip in साराजेवो triggered a राजनयिक संकट जब Austria-Hungary subsequently वितरित an ultimatum to the किंगडम of Serbia.
अनेक alliances formed over the previous decades यहूद invoked.
भीतर weeks, the प्रमुख शक्तियां यहूद at war और, via their colonies, the विरोध जल्द स्प्रेड around the संसार.
On 28 July, the austro-hungarians fired the पहला shots of the युद्ध as preparation लिये the आक्रमण of Serbia.
जबकि the Russians mobilised, the germans invaded न्यूट्रल बेल्जियम and ध्वज on the रास्ता to France, providing a casus belli for ब्रिटेन 's घोषणा of युद्ध विरूद्ध Germany.
After the German कूच on पेरिस थी brought to a halt—the so-called चमत्कार of the marne —the पश्चिमी Front settled into a static battle of attrition साथ a गर्त लकीर that बदला छोटी जबतक 1917.
on the पूर्वी सामने, the Russian army was कामयाब विरूद्ध the austro-hungarians, लकिन थी stopped in its आक्रमण of ईस्ट prussia by the Germans.
in November the Ottoman साम्राज्य joined the war, खोलने up fronts in the काकेशस, Mesopotamia और the sinai.
Italy और Bulgaria went to युद्ध in 1915 and Romania in 1916.
In रूस, the tsar 's government collapsed in कूच 1917 और a subsequent revolution in नवम्बर brought the russians to शर्तें साथ the Central शक्तियां.
After a 1918 German अप्रिय साथ the पश्चिमी front, the allies drove back the Germans in a series of कामयाब offensives and अमरीकी forces began entering the trenches.
Germany, जिससे था its अपना ट्रबल with revolutionaries, सहमत to an armistice on 11 November 1918.
the युद्ध ended in विजय for the Allies.
कार्यक्रम on the घर fronts were as tumultuous as on the बैटल fronts, as the भागीदार tried to mobilize their manpower और आर्थिक संसाधन to लड़ो a कुल युद्ध.
By the समाप्त of the युद्ध, four प्रमुख इम्पीरियल powers—the German, Russian, Austro-Hungarian और उस्मानी empires—ceased to मौजूद.
the successor राज्य of the former two lost a ग्रेट राशि of territory, जबकि the latter दो were dismantled entirely.
The map of सेंट्रल यूरोपीय was redrawn into अनेक छोटी राज्य.
The लीग of राष्ट्र थी formed in the आशा of preventing another such विरोध.
the European राष्ट्रवाद शाखित by the war और the ब्रेकअप of empires, the repercussions of Germany 's defeat और समस्याएं with the सन्धि of Versailles are agreed to be कारकों contributing to संसार युद्ध ii.

दृश्य of defibrillator एलेक्ट्रोड position and अवस्थिति.
defibrillation is a आम उपचार for life-threatening हृदय dysrhythmias, ventricular fibrillation, and pulseless ventricular tachycardia.
defibrillation consists of delivering a therapeutic खुराक of electrical उर्जा to the affected heart साथ a यंत्र पुकारा a defibrillator.
इस depolarizes a नाजुक mass of the दिल मांसपेशी, terminates the dysrhythmia, and allows सामान्य sinus rhythm to be reestablished by the body 's natural pacemaker, in the sinoatrial नोड of the दिल.
Defibrillators can be बाह्य, transvenous, or implanted, depending on the प्रकार of यंत्र प्रयुक्त or needed.
कुछ external units, ज्ञात as automated बाह्य defibrillators ( AEDs ), automate the diagnosis of treatable rhythms, meaning कि lay responders or bystanders are समर्थ to उपयोग उन्हें successfully with छोटी, or in some cases no प्रशिक्षण at सब.
The केटो संस्थान is an American libertarian सोचो टैंक headquartered in वॉशिंगटन, d.c.
It थी founded as the चार्ल्स Koch न्यास in 1974 by Murray rothbard, Ed क्रेन और Charles Koch, chairman of the फलक और मुख्य कार्यपालिका अधिकारी of the संगुटिका koch उद्योग, Inc..
In जुलाई 1976, the name थी बदला to the केटो संस्थान.
According to the 2011 Global go to सोचो Tank Index, Cato is the 6th सबसे influential us based सोचो tank, रैंकिंग 3rd in आर्थिक नीति और 2nd in Social Policy.
the संस्थान 's stated मिशन is `` to बढ़ाएँ the understanding of पब्लिक policies based on the सिद्धान्त of सीमित सरकारी, free बाज़ार, व्यक्तिगत स्वतंत्रता, और peace.
the संस्थान होगा उपयोग the most effective means to originate, advocate, प्रचार, और disseminate applicable policy प्रस्ताव that बनाएँ फ़्री, खोलें, and civil समाजों in the संयुक्त राज्य और throughout the संसार. ''
Cato scholars यहूद नाजुक of जार्ज W. Bush 's रिपब्लिकन administration ( 2001–2009 ) on अनेक issues, सहित the इराकी War, सिविल liberties, शिक्षा, agriculture, energy नीति, and excessive सरकारी बिता.
On अन्य मुद्दे, they समर्थित बुश प्रशासन initiatives, सबसे notably स्वास्थ्य परवाह, Social Security, वैश्विक वार्मिंग, tax नीति, and immigration.
दौरान the 2008 u.S. presidential चुनाव, केटो विद्वानों criticized दोनो major-party candidates, John मैक्केन और बराक ओबामा.
केटो रै criticized President ओबामा 's stances on नीति मुद्दे चूंकि उसके उद्घाटन, ऐसे as फिस्कल stimulus, healthcare reform, विदेशी policy, and the युद्ध on Drugs, जबकि supporting उसके stance on the repeal of Do n't Ask, Do n't बताना and उदार आव्रजन नीति.
ड्रैकुला is an 1897 Gothic हॉरर अनोखा by आयरिश author ब्राम Stoker.
प्रसिद्ध लिये introducing the अक्षर of the पिशाच Count ड्रैकुला, the novel tells the स्टोरी of ड्रैकुला 's attempt to relocate इससे Transylvania to England, और the बैटल between ड्रैकुला और a small समूह of men and महिलाओं led by Professor Abraham Van helsing.
ड्रैकुला रै महरूम आबंटित to अनेक literary जाति सहित पिशाच साहित्य, हॉरर fiction, the गोथिक अनोखा and invasion साहित्य.
The अनोखा छू on themes ऐसे as the भूमिका of women in विक्टोरियन संस्कृति, यौन प्रथाओं, immigration, उपनिवेशवाद, और post-colonialism.
हालांकि Stoker did not invent the पिशाच, he defined इसके आधुनिक form, और the अनोखा रै शाखित numerous theatrical, film and टेलीविज़न interpretations.
Quidditch is a competitive खेल in the wizarding संसार of the हैरी Potter universe, और is from the श्रेणी of children 's novels और movies.

in the Harry कुम्हार universe, Quidditch holds a fervent following similar to the position कि संघ फ़ुटबॉल holds as a globally लोकप्रिय खेल.

the United राज्य कॉंग्रेस is the bicameral legislature of the federal government of the संयुक्त States consisting of दो houses : the lower house ज्ञात as the House of Representatives और the अपर हाउस ज्ञात as the सीनेट.
कॉंग्रेस meets in the कैपिटल in वॉशिंगटन, d.c.
दोनो representatives और senators हैं चुनी through सीधा election.
Congress has a कुल of 535 voting सदस्यों : 435 सदस्यों in the House of प्रतिनिधि और 100 सदस्यों in the सीनेट.
सदस्यों of the हाउस of प्रतिनिधि serve two-year शर्तें representing the लोगों of a ज़िला.
congressional districts हैं apportioned to राज्य by population using the संयुक्त States Census परिणाम, each state in the union having at least एक representative in the हाउस of Representatives.
regardless of population, प्रत्येक of the 50 राज्य has two senators ; the 100 सीनेटरों प्रत्येक serve a six-year term.
the शर्तें are staggered so प्रत्येक दो सालो लगभग one-third of the Senate is up लिये election.
प्रत्येक staggered group of one-third of the सीनेटरों हैं पुकारा 'classes '.
No राज्य of the संयुक्त States रै two senators इससे the same क्लास.
सबसे incumbents seek re-election, and their ऐतिहासिक likelihood of जीतना subsequent चुनावों exceeds 90 percent.
in August 2012, a gallup poll reported that Congress’s approval दरजा amongst Americans was at 10 %, मिलान a 38-year low पहुँचे in नवम्बर 2011.

in अर्थशास्त्र, the demand curve is the आलेख depicting the संबंध between the price of a निश्चित कमोडिटी और the amount of it that उपभोक्ता हैं willing and समर्थ to purchase at कि दिए दाम.
it is a ग्राफिक प्रतिनिधित्व of a माँग अनुसूची.
the माँग curve for all उपभोक्ता साथ फ़ॉलो from the माँग वक्र of every व्यक्तिगत consumer : the व्यक्तिगत demands at each price हैं added together.
Demand वक्र are प्रयुक्त to estimate behaviors in प्रतिस्पर्धी बाज़ार, and हैं प्रायः संयुक्त with सप्लाई वक्र to estimate the संतुलन दाम ( the price at which sellers together हैं willing to sell the वही amount as buyers together हैं willing to ख़रीदे, also ज्ञात as मार्केट clearing दाम ) and the संतुलन मात्रा ( the राशि of that शुभ or service कि होगा be उत्पादित and खरीदा बगैर surplus/excess supply or shortage/excess माँग ) of कि market.
In a monopolistic मार्केट, the demand curve facing the monopolist is simply the market demand curve.
Historia
by nikolaos gysis ( 1892 )
History ( इससे Greek - historia, meaning `` पूछताछ, knowledge acquired by छानबीन '' ) is an umbrella term कि relates to पास्ट events as well as the discovery, संग्रहण, organization, और presentation of information परिचय these events.
The पद includes लौकिक, geologic, and सशुल्क history, लकिन is often generically implied to mean इंसान इतिहास.
Scholars who write परिचय history हैं पुकारा इतिहासकारों.
History can भी refer to the academic अनुशासन जिससे uses a narrative to examine and analyse a sequence of पास्ट events, और objectively determine the पैटर्न of कारण और effect कि determine उन्हें.
इतिहासकारों sometimes debate the nature of इतिहास और इसके उपयोगिता by discussing the पढ़ाई of the अनुशासन as an समाप्त in itself and as a रास्ता of providing `` perspective '' on the समस्याएं of the present.
Stories आम to a particular संस्कृति, लकिन नहीं समर्थित by external स्त्रोत ( such as the किस्से surrounding King आर्थर ) are प्रायः classified as सांस्कृतिक विरासत or महापुरूष, क्युकी they do not support the `` disinterested investigation '' required of the discipline of history.
Events occurring prior to लिखा रिकार्ड हैं considered prehistory.
Herodotus, a 5th सदी b.c. Greek historian is considered within the Western परंपरा to be the `` पिता of history '', and, along with उसके contemporary Thucydides, helped रूप the foundations लिये the आधुनिक पढ़ाई of इंसान history.
Their कार्य continues to be पढ़ा today और the divide between the culture-focused हिरोडोटस and the military-focused Thucydides remains a point of contention or approach in आधुनिक historical लिखने.
in the पूर्वी tradition, a राज्य वृत्तान्त the वसन्त और पतझड़ Annals was known to be compiled इससे as जल्दी as 722 bce although तभी 2nd सदी bce ग्रन्थ survived.
प्राचीन influences have helped spawn variant interpretations of the प्रकृति of history which have evolved over the centuries and continue to change आज.
the आधुनिक पढ़ाई of इतिहास is wide-ranging, और includes the study of विशिष्ट regions और the पढ़ाई of निश्चित topical or thematical elements of ऐतिहासिक छानबीन.
प्रायः history is सिखाया as भाग of primary and द्वितीयक शिक्षा, और the अकादमिक study of इतिहास is a major discipline in विश्वविद्यालयों studies.
मैल्कम x ( ; May 19, 1925february 21, 1965 ), born मैल्कम Little and also ज्ञात as el-hajj malik El-Shabazz ( ), was an African-American Muslim मंत्री and इंसान अधिकारों activist.

Detractors accused उसे of उपदेश racism, ब्लैक सर्वोच्चता, and हिंसा.
He has महरूम called one of the greatest और most influential अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी in इतिहास.
Malcolm x 's पिता died—killed by white supremacists, it was rumored—when he थी यंग, और at least एक of उसके uncles was lynched.
जब he थी 13, his माँ थी लगाई in a दिमागी hospital, और he was placed in a series of foster homes.

मैल्कम X 's expressed beliefs changed substantially over time.

बाद तोड़कर साथ the Nation of islam in 1964—saying of his association साथ it, `` i किया many बाते as a [ ब्लैक ] Muslim that i 'm sorry for अभी.
i was a प्रेत तब... pointed in a certain दिशा और told to march '' —and becoming a Sunni मुस्लिम, he disavowed जातिवाद और expressed willingness to work साथ सिविल rights leaders, he continued to emphasize pan-africanism, black self-determination, और self-defense.

a आभासी यंत्र ( VM ) is a तन्त्र implemented abstraction of the underlying हार्डवेयर, which is प्रस्तुत to the application परत of the प्रणाली.

मकड़ियों ( अनुक्रम araneae ) हैं air-breathing arthropods कि have eight टाँगे and chelicerae साथ fangs that इंजेक्ट venom.
वे are the largest order of arachnids और रैंक सातवाँ in total प्रजाति diversity among all अन्य समूह of जीवों.
मकड़ियों हैं found विश्वव्यापी on प्रत्येक continent मगर लिये अंटार्कटिक, and have become स्थापित in nearly every आवास साथ the एक्सेप्शन of एयर और sea colonization.
As of 2008, at तनिक 43,678 मकड़ी species, और 109 परिवारों have been recorded by taxonomists ; however, वहीँ रै been confusion within the scientific जातियाँ as to कैसा all ये परिवारों चाहिए be वर्गीकृत, as evidenced by the over 20 अलग classifications कि have महरूम proposed since 1900.
Anatomically, मकड़ियों differ इससे other arthropods in that the usual देह खण्ड हैं fused into दो tagmata, the cephalothorax और उदर, और joined by a small, बेलनाकार pedicel.
Unlike insects, मकड़ियों do नहीं have antennae.
In all मगर the most आदिम समूह, the mesothelae, spiders have the most centralized nervous systems of all arthropods, as सब उनके ganglia हैं fused into एक द्रव्यमान in the cephalothorax.
नापसंद सबसे arthropods, spiders have no extensor मांसपेशियां in उनके limbs और instead extend them by hydraulic pressure.
Their abdomens bear appendages कि have महरूम परिवर्धित into spinnerets कि extrude रेशा from up to छह प्रकार of रेशा ग्रंथियों within their उदर.
मकड़ी webs vary widely in आकार, आकार and the amount of स्टिकी thread used.
It अभी appears कि the spiral orb वेब may be एक of the earliest फ़ॉर्म, and मकड़ियों कि produce उलझे cobwebs हैं more abundant और diverse than orb-web spiders.
Spider-like arachnids साथ silk-producing spigots appeared in the Devonian period परिचय, लकिन these animals जाहिर lacked spinnerets.
सच्चा spiders have been found in Carboniferous rocks इससे, और हैं very similar to the most primitive surviving order, the Mesothelae.
The प्रमुख groups of modern मकड़ियों, mygalomorphae और araneomorphae, first appeared in the triassic period, before.
a herbivorous प्रजाति, bagheera kiplingi, थी वर्णित in 2008, लकिन all अन्य ज्ञात प्रजाति हैं परभक्षी, ज़्यादातर preying on कीट और on other मकड़ियों, although a few विशाल प्रजाति भी लो birds and lizards.
Spiders use a चौड़ी range of रणनीति to कैप्चर prey : trapping it in स्टिकी webs, lassoing it साथ स्टिकी bolas, mimicking the prey to avoid detection, or कार्यशील it down.
Most detect शिकार मुख्यतः by संवेदन कंपन, लकिन the क्रियाशील hunters have अधि दृष्टि, और hunters of the genus Portia show लक्षण of intelligence in उनके choice of tactics और क्षमता to develop नई ones.
मकड़ियों ' guts are too सीमित to लो solids, और वे liquidize उनके खाना by flooding it with digestive enzymes and पीस it साथ the bases of their pedipalps, as they do not have सच्चा जबड़े.
पुरूष spiders identify themselves by a variety of complex courtship संस्कार to avoid being eaten by the females.
males of सबसे प्रजाति survive a few matings, limited मुख्यतः by उनके छोटी life spans.
महिलाओं weave रेशा egg-cases, each of जिससे may contain सैंकड़ों of अंडे.
महिलाओं of अनेक प्रजाति care for their young, लिये उदाहरण by carrying उन्हें around or by sharing food साथ them.
a अल्पसंख्यक of प्रजाति हैं social, भवन सांप्रदायिक webs कि may हाउस anywhere from a few to 50,000 individuals.
Social behavior ranges from precarious toleration, as in the widow spiders, to co-operative शिकार and food-sharing.
हालांकि सबसे मकड़ियों live लिये at सबसे दो सालो, tarantulas और अन्य mygalomorph मकड़ियों can सजीव up to 25 years in captivity.
जबकि the venom of a few species is dangerous to इंसानो, वैज्ञानिकों are now researching the उपयोग of spider venom in आयुर्विज्ञान and as non-polluting pesticides.
मकड़ी silk provides a संयोजन of lightness, शक्ति and लोच कि is श्रेष्ठ to that of synthetic सामग्री, and मकड़ी silk genes have महरूम inserted into स्तनधारियों and पौधे to see if ये can be प्रयुक्त as silk कारखानों.
As a result of उनके चौड़ी दायरा of व्यवहार, मकड़ियों have become आम प्रतीकों in art and mythology symbolizing various combinations of सब्र, cruelty और रचनात्मक powers.

household आय is a measure commonly प्रयुक्त by the United राज्य सरकारी और private institutions.
प्रत्येक household is measured by the income of प्रत्येक resident over the आयु of 15.
Income शामिल मजदूरी and salaries, बेरोजगारी insurance, विकलांगता भुगतान, चाइल्ड support भुगतान प्राप्त, नियमित rental रसीदें, as well as कोई निजी कारोबार, निवेश, or अन्य kinds of income प्राप्त routinely.
While inflation-adjusted ( `` real '' ) household आय था महरूम increasing लगभग every साल इससे 1945 to 1999, it has चूंकि महरूम flat and भी decreased recently.
U.S. median household income गिरी इससे $ 51,144 in 2010 to $ 50,502 in 2011.
Extreme गरीबी in the संयुक्त राज्य, अर्थ households जीना on less than $ 2 प्रति day पहले सरकारी लाभ, doubled from 1996 to 1.5 लाख households in 2011, सहित 2.8 million children.
The निवासियों of the household do नहीं have to be सम्बन्धित to the head of the household लिये their आय to be माना part of the household 's income.
as households tend to share a similar आर्थिक कॉन्टेक्स्ट, the उपयोग of household आय remains among the most widely accepted measures of आय.
कि the आकार of a household is नहीं commonly taken into खाता in ऐसे measures may distort कोई analysis of fluctuations भीतर or among the household income categories, और may render direct comparisons between quintiles मुश्किल or भी नामुमकिन.
A पंजीकृत agent, भी ज्ञात as a निवासी एजेंट or statutory agent, in संयुक्त राज्य कारोबार law, is a कारोबार or व्यक्तिगत designated to प्राप्त सेवा of प्रक्रम ( SOP ) जब a कारोबार एंटिटी is a party in a legal कार्रवाई such as a मुकदमा or समन.
The पंजीकृत एजेंट 's पता may also be जहाँ the राज्य will भेजें the कागजी for the yearly नवीकरण of the कारोबार एंटिटी 's चार्टर.
the registered एजेंट लिये a कारोबार entity may be an individual member of the कम्पनी, or ( अधिक often ) a तीसरा party, ऐसे as the संगठन 's वकील or a service company.
Failure to properly maintain a registered एजेंट can affect a कम्पनी negatively.

`` Life, स्वतंत्रता, and the pursuit of Happiness '' is a well-known phrase in the संयुक्त राज्य Declaration of स्वतंत्रता.
The phrase is meant to exemplify the `` unalienable rights '' with जिससे all इंसान beings हैं endowed by उनके निर्माता लिये their सुरक्षा of जिससे वे संस्थान governments.

Classical तलवारबाजी उपयोग the same तीन weapons, लकिन approaches तलवारबाजी as a martial art.
Competitive तलवारबाजी is one of पाँच sports जिससे रै महरूम featured at प्रत्येक एक of the आधुनिक Olympic खेल, the अन्य four होने एथलेटिक्स, साइकिलिंग, Swimming, and जिमनास्टिक्स.
the quadriceps femoris ( Latin for `` four-headed मांसपेशी of the femur `` ), भी पुकारा simply the quadriceps, quadriceps extensor, quads, is a विशाल मांसपेशी समूह कि includes the चार प्रचलित मांसपेशियां on the front of the जांघ.
It is the great extensor मांसपेशी of the घुटना, forming a विशाल मांसल mass जिससे covers the सामने and पहलू of the femur.
The proper Latin plural form of the adjective quadriceps होता be quadricipites.
in आधुनिक English उपयोग, quadriceps is प्रयुक्त in both singular और बहुवचन.
The एकवचन form quadricep, उत्पादित by hypercorrection, is frequently प्रयुक्त.
rms टाइटैनिक was a British यात्री लाइनर कि sank in the North अटलांटिक Ocean on 15 April 1912 बाद colliding साथ an हिमशैल during उसके maiden voyage इससे Southampton, UK to नई York City, US.
the sinking of टाइटैनिक caused the deaths of 1,502 लोगों in एक of the deadliest peacetime मेरीटाइम disasters in modern इतिहास.
the rms टाइटैनिक थी the largest ship afloat at the समय of उसके maiden voyage.
वो was the दूसरी of three ओलम्पिक क्लास ocean liners operated by the White स्टार लकीर, and वो थी निर्मित by the Harland और Wolff डॉकयार्ड in Belfast with थामस Andrews, जो perished साथ the जलयान, as उसके नवल architect.
on उसके maiden voyage, वो carried 2,224 passengers and क्रू.
अंतर्गत the command of एडवर्ड Smith, उसके passengers शामिल कुछ of the wealthiest people in the संसार, as खूब as सैंकड़ों of emigrants from ग्रेट Britain और आयरलैंड, Scandinavia and elsewhere throughout यूरोपीय seeking a new जीवन in North America.
The जलयान was designed to be the पिछला word in सुकून और luxury, साथ an on-board gymnasium, तैराकी पूल, libraries, high-class रेस्तरां and opulent cabins.
वो भी had a powerful wireless telegraph provided लिये the convenience of यात्री as well as लिये operational use.
हालांकि she था advanced सुरक्षा सुविधाएँ ऐसे as watertight compartments और remotely activated watertight doors, वो lacked पर्याप्त lifeboats to accommodate सब of those सवार.
क्युकी of outdated maritime safety regulations, she carried only enough lifeboats for 1,178 people—slightly अधिक than half of the क्रमांक यात्राएं on the maiden voyage, and one-third उसके कुल यात्री and क्रू capacity.
बाद leaving Southampton on 10 अप्रैल 1912, टाइटैनिक called at cherbourg in फ़्रांस और queenstown ( now Cobh ) in आयरलैंड पहले heading westwards towards New York.
on 14 अप्रैल 1912, four दिनों into the क्रासिंग and परिचय 375 मील ( 600 km ) south of न्यूफ़ाउंडलैंड, she hit an हिमशैल at 11:40 pm ship 's समय.
The glancing collision caused titanics हल plates to बकल inwards along her starboard side और खोली five of उसके सोलह watertight compartments to the sea ; the ship gradually भर with water.
Meanwhile, यात्री और some क्रू members यहूद evacuated in lifeboats, अनेक of जिससे यहूद शुभारम्भ तभी partly loaded.
a अनुपातहीन क्रमांक of men were left aboard क्युकी of a `` महिलाओं और children first `` प्रोटोकॉल followed by some of the अधिकारियों loading the lifeboats.
by 2:20 AM, वो broke अलावा and foundered, with खूब over एक thousand people still सवार.
बस अंतर्गत दो घंटों बाद the टाइटैनिक foundered, the cunard लाइनर RMS carpathia arrived on the झाँकी of the डूब, where she brought सवार an estimated 705 survivors.
the disaster was greeted with विश्वव्यापी शॉक और outrage at the विशाल loss of जीवन और the नियामक और operational असफलताओं कि था led to it.
पब्लिक inquiries in Britain और the संयुक्त राज्य led to प्रमुख सुधार in मेरीटाइम सुरक्षा.
एक of उनके सबसे important legacies थी the establishment in 1914 of the अंतरराष्ट्रीय सम्मेलन लिये the सुरक्षा of जीवन at समुद्र ( SOLAS ), जिससे still governs मेरीटाइम सुरक्षा आज.
additionally, अनेक नई बेतार regulations यहूद passed around the world in an effort to learn from the many missteps in बेतार communications -- -which could have saved अनेक अधिक यात्री.
अनेक of the survivors lost all of their धन and possessions और were left अक्षम ; many परिवारों, particularly those of crew सदस्यों from southampton, खोया their प्राथमिक bread-winners.
वे were helped by an outpouring of पब्लिक सहानुभूति और charitable donations.
Some of the पुरूष survivors यहूद accused of कायरता लिये leaving the जलयान जबकि लोगों यहूद still on फलक ; the श्वेत Star लकीर 's अध्यक्ष, J. Bruce Ismay, faced सोशल ostracism for the rest of उसके life.

The इंसान लेग is the संपूर्ण निम्नतर extremity or limb of the human देह, सहित the पैर, जांघ and भी the हिप or gluteal region ; however, the precise परिभाषा in इंसान anatomy refers तभी to the खण्ड of the निम्नतर limb extending इससे the knee to the ankle.

जेम्स Madison, jr. ( March 16, 1751 ( o.s. March 5 ) – जून 28, 1836 ) थी an अमरीकी statesman and राजनैतिक theorist, the चौथी अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य ( 1809–1817 ).
he is hailed as the “father of the constitution” लिये being इंस्ट्रूमेंटल in the drafting of the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान और as the key champion और author of the संयुक्त राज्य विधेयक of अधिकारों.
He परोसा as a politician much of उसके adult जीवन.
बाद the constitution था महरूम drafted, मैडिसन became एक of the नेताओ in the गति to ratify it.
उसके सहयोग साथ सिकंदर Hamilton and जॉन jay उत्पादित the federalist Papers ( 1788 ).
Circulated तभी in New York at the time, वे होता बाद be considered among the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण polemics in support of the Constitution.
He थी भी a delegate to the वर्जिनिया constitutional ratifying convention, and थी इंस्ट्रूमेंटल to the कामयाब ratification effort in Virginia.
जैसे most of उसके contemporaries, मैडिसन changed उसके राजनैतिक दृश्य दौरान उसके life.
दौरान the drafting और ratification of the constitution, he favored a दमदार नेशनल सरकारी, हालांकि later he grew to favor stronger राज्य सरकारें, before settling between the two extremes लेट in उसके life.
in 1789, Madison became a leader in the नई House of Representatives, drafting अनेक मौलिक कानून.
He is notable for drafting the पहला टेन amendments to the संविधान, और thus is ज्ञात as the `` Father of the विधेयक of Rights ``.
मैडिसन worked closely साथ अध्यक्ष George Washington to व्यवस्थित the नई संघीय सरकारी.
Breaking साथ हैमिल्टन and कया became the Federalist Party in 1791, मैडिसन और थामस जेफरसन व्यवस्थित कया वे पुकारा the Republican पार्टी ( बाद पुकारा by इतिहासकारों the Democratic-Republican पार्टी )
as Jefferson’s Secretary of राज्य ( 1801–1809 ), मैडिसन supervised the louisiana Purchase, जिससे doubled the nation’s size.
After उसके election to the प्रेसिडेंसी, he presided over नवीनीकृत prosperity लिये अनेक सालो.
as अध्यक्ष ( 1809–17 ), बाद the विफलता of राजनयिक protests and a व्यापार embargo विरूद्ध ग्रेट ब्रिटेन, he led the nation into the युद्ध of 1812.
he थी responding to अंग्रेजों encroachments on अमरीकी सम्मान and अधिकारों ; in जोड, he चाही to end the influence of the अंग्रेजों among उनके Indian allies, जिनकी प्रतिरोध अवरोधित United States उपनिवेश in the मिडवेस्ट around the Great Lakes.
मैडिसन मिला the war to be an प्रशासनिक दुःस्वप्न, as the United States had neither a दमदार army nor वित्तीय प्रणाली ; as a परिणाम, he afterward supported a stronger नेशनल सरकारी और a दमदार सैन्य, as खूब as the national bank, which he था long opposed.
जैसे अन्य वर्जिनिया कूटनीतिज्ञों in the स्लेव समाज, he थी a slaveholder जो inherited उसके plantation ज्ञात as montpelier, and स्वामित्व सैंकड़ों of स्लेव दौरान उसके आजीवन to cultivate तम्बाकू और other crops.
मैडिसन supported the three-fifths सुलह that allowed three-fifths of the enumerated जनसांख्यिकी of slaves to be गिने लिये representation.

Hydraulic fluids, भी पुकारा हाइड्रोलिक liquids, are the medium by which शक्ति is transferred in हाइड्रोलिक मशीनरी.
आम हाइड्रोलिक fluids हैं आधारित on खनिज आयल or जल.
Examples of equipment that might उपयोग hydraulic fluids शामिल excavators और backhoes, hydraulic brakes, शक्ति परिचालन systems, ट्रांसमिशन, garbage trucks, वायुयान flight control systems, lifts, and औद्योगिक machinery.
Hydraulic प्रणालियों जैसे the ones mentioned above होगा कार्य most efficiently if the हाइड्रोलिक द्रव प्रयुक्त रै no compressibility

महिंद्रा Tractors, the farm equipment प्रभाग of Mahindra & महिंद्रा, builds और स्त्रोत tractors कि are बेची विश्वव्यापी आरपार six महाद्वीपों.
महिंद्रा is also among the top तीन ट्रैक्टर निर्माताओं in the संसार.
महिंद्रा has a विशाल उपभोक्ता आधार in India, चीन और अमेरिका और a growing base in ऑस्ट्रेलिया.

महिंद्रा Tractors साथ sales of nearly 85,000 इकाई annually is one of the largest ट्रैक्टर companies in the world, और is number one in बिक्री in इण्डिया - the largest tractor मार्केट in the world.

the American मध्य क्लास is a सोशल class in the United States.
जबकि the अवधारणा is typically अस्पष्ट in लोकप्रिय राय और आम भाषा उपयोग, समकालीन सोशल scientists have put आगे several, अधिक or कम congruent, theories on the American मध्य class.
Depending on class मॉडल प्रयुक्त, the मध्य class may constitute anywhere from 25 % to 66 % of households.
एक of the पहला प्रमुख अध्ययन of the मध्य क्लास in America थी श्वेत कॉलर : The American मध्य Classes, प्रकाशित in 1951 by sociologist C. राइट wright_mills Mills wright_mills.
बाद sociologists such as Dennis गिल्बर्ट of हैमिल्टन कॉलेज commonly divide the middle क्लास into two sub-groups.
Constituting roughly 15 % to 20 % of households is the upper or पेशेवर मध्य क्लास consisting of अत्यधिक educated, salaried professionals और प्रबंधक.
Constituting roughly एक तीसरा of households is the निम्नतर middle क्लास consisting ज़्यादातर of semi-professionals, skilled कारीगरों और lower-level प्रबन्धन.
Middle-class व्यक्तियों commonly have a comfortable मानक of living, significant आर्थिक security, considerable work स्वायत्तता and rely on their expertise to sustain themselves.
Members of the मध्य क्लास belong to विविध समूह जिससे overlap साथ प्रत्येक अन्य.
Overall, middle-class persons, विशेषकर upper-middle-class individuals, हैं characterized by conceptualizing, creating और consulting.
यूँ, college education is one of the main indicators of middle-class औकात.
largely attributed to the nature of middle-class occupations, middle class values tend to emphasize independence, adherence to मूलभूत standards, valuing नवीनता and respecting non-conformity.
नीतियां more क्रियाशील than other demographics, college शिक्षित मध्य क्लास पेशेवर हैं विभाजित between the दो प्रमुख पार्टियों.
Income varies considerably इससे निकट the नेशनल median to खूब in excess of $ 100,000.
household income आंकड़े, however, do नहीं सदा reflect class औकात and standard of जीना, as they are largely बहकावे by the number of आय earners and fail to recognize household size.
it is इसलिए possible लिये a विशाल, dual-earner, lower middle class household to out-earn a छोटी, one-earner, अपर middle class household.
The middle classes are बहुत influential, as वे encompass the बहुमत of voters, writers, teachers, पत्रकारों, और सम्पादक.
सबसे societal रुझान in the us originate भीतर the मध्य classes.

a विपत्ति is a natural or man-made ( or technological ) जोखिम resulting in an इवेंट of substantial extent causing significant physical क्षति or destruction, loss of life, or drastic change to the पर्यावरण.
A disaster can be ostensively पारिभाषित as कोई tragic इवेंट stemming इससे कार्यक्रम ऐसे as earthquakes, floods, catastrophic accidents, fires, or विस्फोट.
It is a घटना कि can cause damage to जीवन और property और नष्ट the economic, social and सांस्कृतिक जीवन of people.
in समकालीन academia, आपदाओं हैं seen as the consequence of inappropriately प्रबंधित risk.
ये risks हैं the product of a combination of both hazard/s और vulnerability.
Hazards that strike in क्षेत्रों साथ कम vulnerability होगा never become आपदाओं, as is the मामला in uninhabited regions.
विकासशील देशों suffer the महानतम लागत when a विपत्ति hits – अधिक than 95 percent of सब deaths caused by आपदाओं occur in developing countries, और losses due to natural disasters हैं 20 times वृहद ( as a प्रतिशत of जीडीपी ) in विकासशील countries than in industrialized देशों.
in कम्प्यूटिंग, booting ( also known as booting up ) is the आरंभिक नियत of operations कि a computer system performs जब विद्युत शक्ति to the CPU is switched on.
the प्रक्रम begins जब a computer is turned on for the first समय or is re-energized बाद being turned बंद, and ends when the कंप्यूटर is तैयार to perform its normal परिचालन.
on modern general purpose कंप्यूटर, इस can लो tens of सेकेंड और typically involves performing a power-on self-test, locating and initializing परिधीय devices, and तब finding, लदान and starting an ऑपरेटिंग system.
अनेक कंप्यूटर प्रणालियों भी allow these परिचालन to be initiated by a तन्त्र कमांड बगैर साइकिलिंग शक्ति, in what is known as a नरम रिबूट, though कुछ of the आरंभिक परिचालन might be skipped on a नरम reboot.
a बूट loader is a कंप्यूटर कार्यक्रम कि loads the main ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली or runtime environment लिये the computer बाद पूर्णता of the self-tests.
the computer पद बूट is short लिये bootstrap or बूटस्ट्रैप load and derives from the phrase to pull oneself up by one 's bootstraps.
The usage calls ध्यान to the आवश्यकता that, if most software is loaded onto a कंप्यूटर by other तन्त्र already कार्यशील on the computer, कुछ यांत्रिकी must मौजूद to load आरंभिक तन्त्र onto the कंप्यूटर.
जल्दी computers प्रयुक्त a किस्में of ad-hoc विधि to get a छोटी program into memory to solve this प्रॉब्लम.
the आविष्कार of एकीकृत circuit read-only memory ( ROM ) of various प्रकार हल this विरोधाभास by allowing कंप्यूटर to be shipped with a प्रारंभ up कार्यक्रम that could not be erased.
विकास in the capacity of ROM रै allowed कभी अधिक विस्तृत प्रारंभ up प्रक्रियाओं to be implemented.
on सामान्य purpose कंप्यूटर, the बूट process begins साथ the execution of an initial program stored in बूट roms or read in another फ़ैशन.
In कुछ older कंप्यूटर, the initial program might have महरूम the application to run, if no ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली थी प्रयुक्त, or the ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली.
in other computers, the आरंभिक कार्यक्रम is a boot लोडर that may तब लोड into random-access मेमोरी ( RAM ), from nonvolatile secondary भंडार ( ऐसे as a मुश्किल डिस्क drive ) or, in कुछ पुरानी कंप्यूटर, इससे a मीडियम such as punched cards, punched टेप, or चुम्बकीय tape in पुरानी computers, the शब्दकोष कोड of an operating प्रणाली or runtime environment and तब execute it.
if the boot loader is limited in इसके आकार और सामर्थ्य, it may, बजाय, load a larger और more capable द्वितीयक बूट लोडर, जिससे होता तब लोड the ऑपरेटिंग प्रणाली or runtime पर्यावरण.
कुछ embedded systems do not require a noticeable बूट अनुक्रम to शुरू functioning and जब turned on may simply चलाएं operational programs that are stored in rom.
Firebird is an खोलें source एसक्यूएल relational डेटाबेस management system कि runs on Linux, खिड़कियाँ, और a variety of Unix.

आउटसोर्सिंग is the contracting आउट of an आतंरिक कारोबार प्रक्रम to a third-party संगठन.
the अभ्यास of contracting a business प्रक्रम out to a तीसरा party बल्कि than स्टॉफ it internally is common in the आधुनिक अर्थव्यवस्था.
the पद `` आउटसोर्सिंग '' became popular in the United States निकट the फेरे of the 21st century.
आउटसोर्सिंग sometimes involves transferring कर्मचारी और assets इससे one firm to another, लकिन not सदा.
the definition of आउटसोर्सिंग शामिल दोनो foreign और घरेलू contracting, और sometimes शामिल offshoring, जिससे अर्थात् relocating a कारोबार फलन to another देश.
वित्तीय बचत from निम्नतर अंतरराष्ट्रीय मजदूर rates is a big प्रेरणा लिये outsourcing/offshoring.
The विपरीत of outsourcing is पुकारा insourcing, जिससे entails bringing प्रक्रियाओं handled by third-party firms in-house, और is sometimes संपन्नता via vertical integration.
however, a business can provide a contract service to another business बगैर necessarily insourcing that business प्रक्रम.
Human immunodeficiency वायरस ( hiv ) is a lentivirus ( slowly replicating retrovirus ) कि causes acquired immunodeficiency सिंड्रोम ( एड्स ), a कंडीशन in humans in जिससे progressive failure of the प्रतिरक्षा system allows life-threatening opportunistic infections और cancers to thrive.
संक्रमण with hiv occurs by the ट्रांसफ़र of blood, semen, vaginal fluid, pre-ejaculate, or स्तन मिल्क.
भीतर ये bodily fluids, HIV is उपस्थित as दोनो फ़्री virus अणु and वायरस within संक्रमित immune कोशिकाएं.
hiv infects vital कोशिकाएं in the इंसान प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली such as हेल्पर t cells ( specifically CD4 + T cells ), macrophages, and dendritic कोशिकाएं.
HIV infection लीड to कम levels of CD4+ t कोशिकाएं through a क्रमांक of mechanisms including : apoptosis of uninfected bystander cells, सीधा वाइरल हत्या of infected cells, और हत्या of संक्रमित cd4+ t कोशिकाएं by CD8 cytotoxic lymphocytes that recognize infected cells.
When CD4+ t कोशिका numbers मनाही नीचे a नाजुक स्तर, cell-mediated immunity is lost, और the body becomes progressively more susceptible to opportunistic infections.

a fireman 's pole ( also पुकारा a स्लाइडिंग pole or firepole ) is a लकड़ी pole or a metal ट्यूब or pipe संस्थापित between floors in fire stations, allowing अग्निशमन responding to an alarm to जल्दी descend to the मैदान floor तेज़ than by using a मानक staircase.

Written simlish
Simlish is a fictional भाषा प्रदर्शित in EA खेल ' Sim series of खेल.
it debuted in simcopter, and रै been especially prominent in The सीम, The सीम 2 और The सीम 3.
the सीम विकास टोली created the अद्वितीय Simlish भाषा by experimenting with fractured Ukrainian, फ्रेंच, Latin, Finnish, अंग्रेज़ी, Fijian, सेबुआनो, और tagalog.

Civilized Creatures in spore can भी be सिखाया to बोलो Simlish.

पंक्तियां होगा Wright was conscious of the need for dialogue in the game, लकिन विचार कि using a real भाषा होता मेक it ध्वनि too दोहराए और होता also be too costly to hire अनुवादक लिये संसार languages.

an उदाहरण of अल्ट्रासोनिक Testing ( UT ) on ब्लेड roots of a V2500 iae aircraft इंजन.
Step 1 : the UT जांच is लगाई on the root of the blades to be inspected साथ the सहायता of a खास borescope tool ( video probe ).
कदम 2 : Instrument जमावट हैं इनपुट.
कदम 3 : The probe is scanned over the blade रूट.
In this मामला, an indication ( शिखर in the आंकड़ा ) through the रेड लकीर ( or gate ) indicates a good blade ; an indication to the बाएँ of कि दायरा indicates a क्रैक.
principle of अल्ट्रासोनिक testing.
बाएँ : A probe sends a ध्वनि वेव into a परीक्षण material.
वहीँ are दो indications, एक इससे the initial पल्स of the जांच, and the second due to the वापस वॉल echo.
RIGHT : a defect creates a तीसरा indication और simultaneously reduces the amplitude of the back wall indication.

in ultrasonic परीक्षण ( UT ), बहुत छोटी अल्ट्रासोनिक pulse-waves with center बारंबारता ranging from 0.1-15 mhz और occasionally up to 50 mhz are launched into सामग्री to detect internal खामियां or to characterize सामग्री.
a आम उदाहरण is ultrasonic मोटाई मापन, जिससे tests the thickness of the परीक्षण ऑब्जेक्ट, लिये example, to मॉनिटर pipework corrosion.
अल्ट्रासोनिक testing is प्रायः performed on स्टील and other metals and alloys, though it can also be प्रयुक्त on कंक्रीट, लकडी और composites, albeit साथ कम रेज़ोल्यूशन.
it is a रूप of non-destructive testing प्रयुक्त in अनेक industries सहित aerospace, automotive and other परिवहन सेक्टर.

in आयुर्विज्ञान, ischemia, also spelled as ischaemia or ischæmia, ( ; from यूनानी language ισχαιμία, ischaimía ; isch- रूट denoting a प्रतिबंध or thinning or to मेक or grow thin/lean, haema रक्त ) is a restriction in रक्त supply to ऊतकों, causing a shortage of ऑक्सीजन और glucose needed for cellular चयापचय ( to रखना tissue जिंदा ).
Ischemia is generally caused by problems with रक्त बरतन, साथ resultant damage to or dysfunction of ऊतक.

bas syndrome ( ds ) or Down 's सिंड्रोम, भी known as trisomy 21, is a जेनेटिक disorder caused by the presence of all or part of a तीसरा copy of chromosome 21.
bas syndrome is the सबसे आम chromosome abnormality in humans.
it is typically संबद्ध with a delay in संज्ञानात्मक ability ( दिमागी retardation, or mr ) और physical विकास, और a particular set of facial characteristics.
The average iq of young adults साथ bas सिंड्रोम is around 50, whereas young वयस्कों बगैर the कंडीशन typically have an IQ of 100.
( MR रै historically महरूम पारिभाषित as an iq below 70. )
a विशाल proportion of individuals साथ bas सिंड्रोम have a severe degree of बौद्धिक विकलांगता.
Down सिंड्रोम is नामित बाद जॉन langdon Down, the अंग्रेजों चिकित्सक जो described the सिंड्रोम in 1866.
the condition was clinically वर्णित पहले by जां etienne dominique esquirol in 1838 और Edouard seguin in 1844.
bas syndrome थी पहचाना as a chromosome 21 trisomy by Dr. Jérôme Lejeune in 1959.
Down syndrome can be identified in a baby at जनम or पहले जनम by prenatal screening.
pregnancies with this निदान are प्रायः terminated.
the सीडीसी estimates that about एक of प्रत्येक 691 शिशु born in the संयुक्त States प्रत्येक साल is born साथ Down सिंड्रोम.
अनेक children साथ Down syndrome are educated in नियमित स्कूल classes जबकि others आवश्यकता specialised शैक्षणिक सुविधाएं.
कुछ children ग्रैजुएट from high school, and, in the us, वहीँ हैं increasing अवसर लिये participating in post-secondary education.
शिक्षा और उचित care has been दिखाया to improve विशेषता of जीवन significantly.
अनेक वयस्कों साथ Down सिंड्रोम are समर्थ to work at paid नियुक्ति in the जातियाँ, while others require a अधिक sheltered कार्य environment.

the servicemen 's Readjustment Act of 1944 ( p.l. 78-346, 58 स्टेट. 284m ), known informally as the g.i. Bill, was a law कि provided a दायरा of लाभ लिये returning संसार War II veterans ( commonly referred to as G.I.s ).
लाभ included low-cost mortgages, low-interest लोन to प्रारंभ a कारोबार or farm, cash payments of ट्यूशन and जीना खर्च to attend college, ऊँची स्कूल or वोकेशनल शिक्षा, as well as एक साल of बेरोजगारी compensation.
It was available to प्रत्येक दिग्गज who था been on क्रियाशील ड्यूटी during the युद्ध years for at least ninety दिनों and था not महरूम dishonorably discharged ; combat थी नहीं जरूरी.
By the end of the कार्यक्रम in 1956, roughly 2.2 लाख veterans had प्रयुक्त the g.i. विधेयक education लाभ in अनुक्रम to attend कॉलेजों or विश्वविद्यालयों, and an अतिरिक्त 6.6 लाख used these benefits लिये कुछ kind of प्रशिक्षण कार्यक्रम.
Since the असली 1944 विधि, the term has आइये to शामिल अन्य दिग्गज benefit कार्यक्रम created to assist दिग्गजों of subsequent युद्धों as खूब as peacetime सेवा.
इतिहासकारों and economists consider the g.i. विधेयक a प्रमुख राजनैतिक success—especially in कंट्रास्ट to the उपचार of World युद्ध i veterans—and a प्रमुख contribution to अमेरिका 's भण्डार of इंसान पूंजी that sped long-term आर्थिक growth.
The वाटरगेट scandal was a political कांड that occurred in the United राज्य in the 1970s as a परिणाम of the जून 17, 1972 break-in at the लोकतांत्रिक नेशनल कमेटी headquarters at the Watergate दफ्तर complex in वॉशिंगटन, D.C., and the निक्सन administration 's attempted cover-up of its भागीदारी.
the scandal आखिरकार led to the resignation of रिचर्ड Nixon, the अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States, on अगस्त 9, 1974 — the तभी इस्तीफा of a U.S. अध्यक्ष.
the कांड भी resulted in the indictment, विचारण, conviction, और incarceration of forty-three व्यक्तियों, dozens of whom यहूद निक्सन 's top administration officials.
the affair began with the गिरफ़्तार of five मेन लिये तोड़कर और entering into the Democratic नेशनल कमेटी ( dnc ) headquarters at the Watergate जटिल on जून 17, 1972.
the Federal ब्यूरो of छानबीन ( एफबीआई ) connected नकदी found on the burglars to a slush निधि used by the Committee लिये the re-election of the अध्यक्ष, the official संगठन of Nixon 's campaign.
in जुलाई 1973, as प्रमाण mounted against the president 's स्टाफ, सहित गवाही provided by पूर्व staff सदस्यों in an छानबीन conducted by the Senate Watergate कमेटी, it was नाज़िल कि अध्यक्ष निक्सन था a tape-recording system in his कार्यालयों और he था recorded many बातचीत.
रिकार्डिंग इससे ये टेपों implicated the president, revealing he था attempted to कवर up the questionable ( and illegal ) goings-on कि had लिया place during his administration, both पहले और after the break-in.
After a protracted श्रेणी of bitter अदालत battles, the U.S. Supreme अदालत unanimously शासित that the president had to hand over the tapes to सरकारी investigators ; he ultimately complied.

Elizabeth imogene Webber ( formerly lansing और स्पेंसर ) is a fictional character on the एबीसी Daytime साबुन ओपेरा सामान्य हॉस्पिटल.

the संयुक्त States प्रेसिडेंसी of Ronald Reagan, भी ज्ञात as the Reagan administration, थी a Republican प्रशासन headed by Ronald Reagan इससे जनवरी 20, 1981, to जनवरी 20, 1989.
Domestically, the प्रशासन favored reducing government programs and introduced the largest across-the-board tax कटौती in American history.
the आर्थिक policies enacted in 1981, known as `` reaganomics ``, यहूद an example of supply-side economics.
reagan aimed to प्रोत्साहित उद्यमिता and limit the विकास of सोशल बिता, as खूब as the कटौती of विनियमन और inflation.
Economic विकास saw a दमदार रिकवरी in the 1980s, helping Reagan to win a भूस्खलन re-election.
The नेशनल debt increased significantly, however.
regarding foreign नीति, the administration थी steadfastly anti-communist, कॉलिंग the सोवियत Union an `` दुष्ट साम्राज्य `` and समाप्ति 1970s détente.
Reagan accelerated the विशाल buildup of the सैन्य started by उसके पूर्ववर्ती, including an आक्रमण of हरा, the पहला प्रमुख overseas कार्रवाई by u.S. troops since the समाप्त of the वियतनाम युद्ध.
the `` Reagan Doctrine `` controversially granted सहायता to paramilitary forces seeking to फेकने कम्युनिस्ट governments, particularly in war-torn सेंट्रल अमेरिका and अफगानिस्तान.
reagan भी promoted new technologies ऐसे as मिसाइल defense प्रणालियों in अनुक्रम to confront the soviets and उनके allies.
in diplomacy, Reagan forged a strong गठबंधन साथ uk Prime मंत्री Margaret Thatcher, और he मिले with सोवियत सामान्य सचिव Mikhail Gorbachev चार टाइम्स, aiming to shrink the superpowers ' nuclear arsenals.
reagan 's प्रेसिडेंसी रै महरूम termed the `` Reagan Revolution '', or the आयु of reagan in recognition of the political realignment both within and परे the u.S. in एहसान of उसके ब्रांड of कोसा और उसके आस्था in फ़्री बाज़ार.
The reagan प्रशासन worked toward the collapse of सोवियत साम्यवादी, and it did पतन बस as he बाएँ office.
Victory in the Cold युद्ध led to a unipolar world साथ the u.S. as the world 's एकमात्र महाशक्ति.
जबकि the damaging Iran-Contra affair engulfed अनेक Reagan aides दौरान his दूसरी पद, Reagan खुद बाएँ office with a 63 percent approval rating, एक of the उच्चतर approval ratings of departing presidents.
After सालो of unstinting praise from the सही, और unrelenting आलोचना from the बाएँ, इतिहासकार दाउद हेनरी पाता कि by 2009 a सर्वसम्मति had emerged among विद्वानों कि reagan revived कोसा और turned the स्वदेश to the right by demonstrating a `` pragmatic conservatism '' that promoted विचारधारा within the constraints imposed by the divided राजनैतिक प्रणाली.
Furthermore, says Henry, the सर्वसम्मति viewpoint agrees कि he revived faith in the प्रेसिडेंसी और अमरीकी self-confidence, और contributed critically to ending the ठंडा युद्ध.
Crude death रेट by देश ( 2006 ).
Mortality रेट is a measure of the number of deaths ( in सामान्य, or due to a specific कारण ) in a जनसांख्यिकी.
Scaled to the size of कि जनसांख्यिकी, प्रति ईकाई of समय.
मृत्यु rate is typically expressed in units of मौतों प्रति 1000 individuals प्रति साल ; thus, a मृत्यु रेट of 9.5 ( आउट of 1000 ) in a जनसांख्यिकी of 1,000 would mean 9.5 मौतों per year in कि entire जनसांख्यिकी, or 0.95 % आउट of the total.
it is पृथक from morbidity रेट, जिससे refers to the क्रमांक of individuals in ग़रीब स्वास्थ्य दौरान a दिए time काल ( the prevalence रेट ) or the number of newly appearing मामले of the disease per ईकाई of समय ( incidence rate ).
The term `` मृत्यु `` is also sometimes inappropriately प्रयुक्त to refer to the क्रमांक of मौतों among a set of diagnosed hospital मामले लिये a disease or injury, बल्कि than लिये the सामान्य जनसांख्यिकी of a country or जातीय समूह.
इस disease mortality statistic is अधिक precisely referred to as `` case fatality rate `` ( cfr ).
एक distinguishes:
the crude death रेट, the कुल number of मौतों per year प्रति 1000 people.
the crude मौत rate for the पूरे world is परिचय 8.37 प्रति 1000 per साल according to the वर्तमान सीआईए संसार factbook.
the perinatal mortality रेट, the sum of neonatal मौतों और fetal मौतों ( stillbirths ) प्रति 1000 births.
the maternal मृत्यु ratio, the क्रमांक of maternal deaths प्रति 100,000 सजीव births in same समय period.
the मातृ mortality रेट, the क्रमांक of मातृ deaths प्रति 1,000 महिलाओं of reproductive आयु in the जनसांख्यिकी ( generally defined as 15–44 years of age ).
The शिशु मृत्यु rate, the क्रमांक of मौतों of children less than 1 साल बूढ़ा प्रति 1000 सजीव births.
the चाइल्ड mortality रेट, the क्रमांक of मौतों of children कम than 5 years old प्रति 1000 live births.
the standardised mortality अनुपात ( smr ) - इस represents a आंशिक तुलना to the numbers of deaths that would have been अपेक्षित if the जनसांख्यिकी था महरूम of a standard संयोजन in शर्तें of आयु, gender, इत्यादि.
The age-specific mortality rate ( asmr ) - This refers to the total number of मौतों per साल per 1000 लोगों of a given आयु ( e.g. आयु 62 पिछला जन्मदिवस ).
In लिहाज़ to the or failure of medical उपचार or procedures, एक होता भी distinguish:
The early mortality रेट, the कुल number of मौतों in the जल्दी चरण of an जारी treatment, or in the period तत्काल following an उपचार.
the late mortality रेट, the कुल number of deaths in the लेट stages of an जारी treatment, or a significant लंबाई of समय after an अधि उपचार.
Note कि the crude मौत rate as defined above and लागू to a पूरे जनसांख्यिकी can give a misleading छाप.
The crude मौत रेट depends on the आयु ( and लिंग ) specific मृत्यु दरों और the आयु ( and लिंग ) वितरण of the जनसांख्यिकी.
the number of मौतों प्रति 1000 लोगों can be higher for विकसित राष्ट्र than in less-developed countries, despite life प्रत्याशा being higher in विकसित countries due to standards of स्वास्थ्य being बेहतर.
इस happens क्युकी developed देशों typically have a completely different population age वितरण, साथ a much higher proportion of पुरानी people, due to दोनो lower हाल birth दरों and lower mortality दरों.
a more complete चित्र of मृत्यु is दिए by a life table जिससे shows the mortality रेट separately लिये प्रत्येक आयु.
a life तालिका is जरुरी to दे a शुभ estimate of जीवन प्रत्याशा.
An otoacoustic emission ( oae ) is a ध्वनि which is उत्पन्न from within the inner कान.
having been पूर्वानुमानित by Thomas सुनहरा in 1948, its existence थी first demonstrated experimentally by David kemp in 1978 और otoacoustic emissions have since महरूम दिखाया to उठता by a number of अलग सेल्यूलर mechanisms within the inner ear.
अध्ययन have shown that oaes गायब बाद the inner कान रै महरूम क्षतिग्रस्त, so oaes are प्रायः प्रयुक्त in the प्रयोगशाला and the क्लिनिक as a measure of भीतरी कान स्वास्थ्य.
broadly speaking, there हैं two types of otoacoustic emissions : spontaneous otoacoustic emissions ( soaes ), जिससे can occur बगैर external उत्तेजनाओं, और जगाई otoacoustic emissions ( eoaes ), which आवश्यकता an evoking stimulus.
hurricane टॉमस थी the उन्नीसवीं named तूफ़ान और बारहवीं hurricane of the 2010 Atlantic hurricane season.
Tomas विकसित इससे a tropical वेव ईस्ट of the windward Islands on अक्तूबर 29.
Quickly intensifying into a hurricane, it स्थानांतरित through the windward Islands और passed बहुत near Saint लूसिया.
बाद reaching श्रेणी 2 status on the saffir-simpson स्केल, टॉमस quickly weakened to a तीव्र तूफ़ान in the सेंट्रल caribbean Sea, due to दमदार हवा shear और शुष्क air.
टॉमस बाद regained hurricane status as it reorganized near the windward ड्योढ़ी.
Throughout the hurricane 's path, 71 लोगों are known to have महरूम मारे, 14 of whom were in संत लूसिया.
मौद्रिक losses throughout the windward आइलैंड्स were estimated at us $ 588 लाख, मुख्यतः in संत Lucia.
In the वेक of the तूफ़ान in Haiti, flooding intensified an ongoing cholera outbreak indirectly causing अधिक fatalities.
According to a रपट released in दिसम्बर 2010, 55 people were killed in Cuba और hispanola, हालांकि the distribution of ये fatalities are अनजान.
overall damage इससे the storm was at least $ 741 लाख.

postmodern साहित्य is literature characterized by भारी reliance on तकनीकों जैसे fragmentation, विरोधाभास, and questionable narrators, और is often ( हालांकि नहीं exclusively ) पारिभाषित as a स्टाइल or ट्रेंड जिससे उभरा in the post–world युद्ध ii era.
postmodern works हैं देखी as a प्रतिक्रिया विरूद्ध Enlightenment सोच and modernist approaches to साहित्य.
Postmodern literature, जैसे postmodernism as a whole, tends to resist परिभाषा or वर्गीकरण as a `` गति ''.
बेशक, the अभिसरण of postmodern literature with विभिन्न modes of नाजुक theory, particularly reader-response और deconstructionist approaches, and the subversions of the अव्यक्त अनुबंध between लेखक, टेक्स्ट और reader by जिससे इसके works हैं often characterised, have led to pre-modern fictions such as cervantes ' Don Quixote ( 1605,1615 ) और laurence Sterne 's eighteenth-century व्यंग्य tristram shandy होने retrospectively inducted into the fold.
जबकि वहीँ is little consensus on the precise विशेषताएँ, पैमाना, and importance of postmodern literature, as is often the मामला with कलाकारी movements, postmodern literature is commonly defined in संबंध to a precursor.
For उदाहरण, a postmodern साहित्यिक work tends नहीं to conclude साथ the neatly tied-up समाप्ति as is often found in modernist literature, but प्रायः parodies it.
Postmodern लेखक tend to celebrate मौका over शिल्प, and further employ metafiction to undermine the लेखक 's प्राधिकार.
another characteristic of postmodern साहित्य is the questioning of भेद between ऊँची और कम संस्कृति through the उपयोग of pastiche, the संयोजन of subjects और genres not previously deemed अनुरूप लिये साहित्य.

scooby-doo is an American animated कार्टून मताधिकार, comprising अनेक एनिमेटेड टेलीविज़न series produced from 1969 to the उपस्थित दिन.

the एस्टेट कर in the संयुक्त राज्य is a tax imposed on the ट्रांसफ़र of the `` taxable एस्टेट `` of a deceased person, whether such प्रॉपर्टी is transferred via a होगा, according to the राज्य laws of intestacy or वरना बना as an incident of the मौत of the मालिक, such as a ट्रांसफ़र of प्रॉपर्टी इससे an intestate estate or trust, or the payment of certain जीवन बीमे benefits or वित्तीय खाता रकम to beneficiaries.
The एस्टेट कर is one part of the Unified तोहफा और एस्टेट कर system in the United राज्य.
the other भाग of the प्रणाली, the gift tax, imposes a tax on हस्तांतरण of प्रॉपर्टी दौरान a person 's जीवन ; the तोहफा tax prevents avoidance of the estate कर चाहिए a व्यक्ति want to दे दूर his/her estate.
In addition to the federal सरकारी, अनेक राज्य भी थोपने an एस्टेट कर, साथ the state संस्करण पुकारा either an estate कर or an उत्तराधिकार कर.
प्रतिद्वंद्वियों of the estate tax कॉल it the `` death कर ''.
If an एसेट is left to a spouse or a federally पहचाना दान, the tax usually करता नहीं apply.
in जोड, up to $ 5,250,000 can be दिए by an individual, before and/or upon their death, बगैर incurring federal gift or एस्टेट taxes.

raffaello Sanzio da Urbino ( अप्रैल 6 or कूच 28, 1483 – April 6, 1520 ), बेहतर ज्ञात simply as राफेल, थी an इतालवी चित्रकार और architect of the High Renaissance.
उसके कार्य is admired for its स्पष्टता of form and ease of संयोजन और लिये इसके visual achievement of the neoplatonic आदर्श of इंसान grandeur.
साथ with michelangelo और लियोनार्डो da Vinci, he फ़ॉर्म the traditional trinity of ग्रेट मास्टर्स of कि काल.
राफेल थी enormously productive, कार्यशील an unusually large कार्यशाला, और despite उसके death at 37, a विशाल देह of his कार्य remains.
Many of his works हैं मिला in the वेटिकन राजमहल, जहाँ the frescoed राफेल Rooms यहूद the central, और the largest, कार्य of उसके career.
The बेहतरीन ज्ञात work is the स्कूल of Athens in the वेटिकन Stanza देला segnatura.
बाद उसके जल्दी सालो in Rome much of his कार्य थी self-designed, but लिये the सबसे भाग चलाया by the कार्यशाला from उसके drawings, with considerable घाटा of विशेषता.
He was extremely influential in his आजीवन, हालांकि बाहर रोम उसके work थी ज़्यादातर known इससे उसके collaborative printmaking.
बाद his मौत, the influence of his ग्रेट प्रतिद्वंद्वी michelangelo थी अधिक widespread जबतक the 18th और 19th सदियां, जब Raphael 's more निर्मल और harmonious qualities यहूद again regarded as the उच्चतम मॉडल.
उसके करियर जलप्रपात naturally into three phases and तीन styles, पहला वर्णित by giorgio vasari : उसके early सालो in Umbria, then a period of परिचय चार सालो ( इससे 1504–1508 ) absorbing the artistic परंपराओं of Florence, followed by his last hectic और triumphant twelve years in Rome, working लिये two Popes और their close शरीक.
Julia Fiona रॉबर्ट्स ( born October 28, 1967 ) is an अमरीकी actress.

चिह्नित इलियट Zuckerberg ( born may 14, 1984 ) is an अमरीकी computer प्रोग्रामर और Internet उद्योगों.
he is बेहतरीन ज्ञात as एक of five co-founders of the social नेटवर्किंग जालस्थल फेसबुक.
as of अप्रैल 2013, Zuckerberg is the chairman and मुख्य कार्यपालिका of Facebook, Inc. और in 2013 उसके निजी माल was अनुमानित to be US $ 13.3 अरब.
साथ with उसके college roommates और fellow हार्वर्ड विश्वविद्यालयों students एडुआर्डो Saverin, Andrew McCollum, Dustin Moskovitz and Chris Hughes, zuckerberg launched Facebook from हार्वर्ड 's शयनागार कक्ष.

कमेटी of Ways और अर्थात् is the मुख्य tax -writing committee of the United States House of Representatives.

सोशल Security

The U.S. Constitution requires कि सब bills regarding taxation जरूर originate in the हाउस of प्रतिनिधि.
चूंकि House procedure is कि सब बिल्स regarding कराधान जरूर go through इस कमेटी, the committee is बहुत influential, as is इसके सीनेट बंटवारा, the U.S. सीनेट कमेटी on वित्त.
The तरीके and अर्थात् कमेटी in the 111th कॉंग्रेस थी chaired by चार्ली Rangel, who था लिया a छोड़ of अनुपस्थिति as chairman until हाउस आचार उल्लंघनों यहूद resolved.
However, his leave of अनुपस्थिति as chairman was शासित to be a इस्तीफा.
