डेव शिविर became the कमेटी chair लिये the 112th कॉंग्रेस, बाद the republicans जीती कंट्रोल of the हाउस in the 2010 चुनाव.
The blue व्हेल ( balaenoptera musculus ) is a समुद्री स्तनधारी belonging to the suborder of baleen whales ( called mysticeti ).
At in लंबाई और or अधिक in weight, it is the largest known एनिमल to have कभी existed.
long and slender, the ब्लू व्हेल 's body can be various shades of bluish-grey dorsally और somewhat हल्का underneath.
वहीँ हैं at least three पृथक subspecies : B. m. musculus of the North अटलांटिक and उत्तर प्रशांत, B. m. intermedia of the Southern Ocean and B. m. brevicauda ( भी ज्ञात as the सानो ब्लू whale ) found in the भारतीय समंदर और South प्रशांत समंदर.
B. m. इंडिका, found in the भारतीय समंदर, may be another subspecies.
as with other baleen whales, its आहार consists लगभग exclusively of छोटी crustaceans ज्ञात as krill.
Blue whales यहूद abundant in nearly all the महासागर on धरती जबतक the शुरूआत of the twentieth century.
लिये over a सदी, वे were hunted लगभग to extinction by whalers जबतक protected by the international जातियाँ in 1966.
A 2002 रपट अनुमानित वहीँ were 5,000 to 12,000 ब्लू whales worldwide, स्तिथ in at तनिक पाँच समूह.
अधिक recent research into the सानो subspecies suggests इस may be an underestimate.
पहले whaling, the largest जनसांख्यिकी was in the Antarctic, क्रमांकन लगभग 239,000 ( दायरा 202,000 to 311,000 ).
वहीँ remain only much छोटी ( around 2,000 ) एकाग्रता in each of the पूर्वी उत्तर प्रशांत, Antarctic, और Indian Ocean groups.
वहीँ are दो more groups in the उत्तर अटलांटिक, और at तनिक दो in the Southern Hemisphere.
the ग्लोब artichoke ( cynara cardunculus var. scolymus ) is a किस्में of a species of thistle cultivated as a खाना.
the edible matter is buds that form भीतर the flower heads before the पुष्प आइये into bloom.
the buds go दूर or बदलें to a coarse, मुश्किल edible रूप when the flower blooms.
The uncultivated or जंगली variety of the species is पुकारा a cardoon.
it is a perennial plant native to the भूमध्यसागरीय प्रदेश.
The संयुक्त States एक hundred-dollar bill ( $ 100 ) is a denomination of संयुक्त States currency.
U.S. statesman, inventor, and diplomat Benjamin फ्रैंकलिन is फिलहाल प्रदर्शित on the obverse of the विधेयक.
On the रिवर्स of the banknote is an चित्र of स्वतंत्रता हॉल.
the $ 100 विधेयक is the largest denomination that रै been मुद्रित since July 13, 1969, when the denominations of $ 500, $ 1,000, $ 5,000, and $ 10,000 were retired.
the ब्यूरो of नक्काशी and मुद्रण says the औसत जीवन of a $ 100 bill in परिसंचरण is 90 months ( 7.5 years ) before it is replaced due to पहनें और आंसू.
the बिल्स हैं also commonly referred to as `` Benjamins '', in reference to the use of बेंजामिन फ्रैंकलिन 's पोर्ट्रेट on the denomination, or `` c-notes '', आधारित on the रोमन numeral लिये 100.
the विधेयक is one of दो denominations printed आज that करता not feature a President of the United राज्य ; the other is the $ 10 bill, featuring सिकंदर Hamilton.
the time on the clock of स्वतंत्रता Hall on the रिवर्स, according to the u.S. ब्यूरो of नक्काशी and Printing, shows लगभग 4:10.
One सौ hundred-dollar बिल्स हैं delivered by Federal आरक्षित Banks in mustard-colored straps ( $ 10,000 ).
the Series 2009 $ 100 विधेयक redesign थी अनावरण on अप्रैल 21, 2010, and was to be जारी to the public on फ़रवरी 11, 2011, लकिन उत्पादन was shut down in दिसम्बर 2010 क्युकी as अनेक as 30 % were अनुपयोगी due to a manufacturing flaw.
A लंबवत क्रीज in the paper reveals a blank स्पेस on the bill जब pulled out.
in उनके replacement, and continuing the high demand of इस denomination, the श्रेणी 2006a थी शुभारम्भ retaining the previous डिज़ाइन ( 1996-generation ).
on अप्रैल 24, 2013, the संघीय Reserve घोषित the नई $ 100 bill होता enter circulation on अक्तूबर 8, 2013.

दाउद ( ; ISO 259-3 dawid ; ' ; Strong 's : daveed ) according to the Hebrew बाइबल, थी the second किंग of the United किंगडम of इसराईल, and according to the नई Testament gospels of मैथ्यू और Luke, an ancestor of यीशु.
His life is conventionally दिनाँक to c. 1040–970 bce, his reign over Judah c. 1010–1002 BCE, और उसके शासनकाल over the United Kingdom of Israel c. 1002–970 BCE.
The Books of सैमुएल, 1 किंग्स, and 1 Chronicles हैं the only sources of सूचना on David, although the Tel Dan stele ( दिनाँक c. 850–835 bce ) contains the phrase ( bytdwd ), read as `` House of David '', जिससे most scholars लो as पुष्टि of the existence in the mid-9th सदी BCE of a judean royal dynasty पुकारा the हाउस of दाउद.
He is चित्रित as a righteous किंग, हालांकि नहीं बगैर त्रुटियां, as well as an acclaimed योद्धा, संगीतकार, and कवि, traditionally credited लिये composing many of the psalms contained in the Book of ज़बूर.
दाउद is central to यहूदी, Christian, और Islamic doctrine और culture.
biblical tradition maintains कि a सीधा वंशज of दाउद will be the Messiah.
in islam he is माना to be a prophet और the किंग of a nation.
काठमांडू ( ; ) is the पूंजी and largest शहरी agglomerate of नेपाल.
The agglomerate consists of काठमांडू महानगर नगर at its कोर, and इसके sister शहरों patan, Kirtipur, Thimi, and Bhaktapur.
It also includes the recently पहचाना शहरी क्षेत्रों of shankhapur, Karyabinayak, और champapur.
banepa, Dhulikhel, and panauti हैं satellite urban areas of काठमांडू located बस बाहर the Kathmandu घाटी.
Kathmandu is also ज्ञात informally as `` ktm '' or the `` tri-city ''.
according to a जनसांख्यिकी conducted in 2011, Kathmandu metropolis alone रै 975,453 inhabitants ; and the agglomerate रै a जनसांख्यिकी of more than 2.5 million निवासियों.
The महानगर नगर क्षेत्रफल is और रै a जनसांख्यिकी density of 19,250 per km2.
the नगर स्टैंड at an उन्नयन of लगभग in the bowl-shaped Kathmandu घाटी of central नेपाल.
It is surrounded by four major mountains : shivapuri, Phulchoki, nagarjun, और चंद्रगिरि.
काठमांडू घाटी is भाग of तीन जिले ( काठमांडू, ललितपुर, और भक्तपुर ), रै the highest जनसांख्यिकी घनत्व in the country, और is घर to परिचय a twelfth of नेपाल 's जनसांख्यिकी.
दौरान rana और शाह eras, the नाम `` नेपाल '' referred तभी to the काठमांडू Valley ; it थी कया people जो जिया outside the घाटी पुकारा it.
During इस काल, अंग्रेजों इतिहासकारों पुकारा the घाटी itself `` नेपाल Proper ''.
आज, काठमांडू is not only the capital of the संघीय लोकतांत्रिक गणतंत्र of नेपाल, but भी the मुख्यालय of the Central Development Region of नेपाल.
the सेंट्रल प्रदेश comprises three zones : bagmati, narayani, और Janakpur.
Kathmandu is स्तिथ in the bagmati Zone.
Kathmandu is the gateway to पर्यटन in नेपाल.
it is भी the nerve बीच of the देश 's अर्थव्यवस्था.
it has the most उन्नत infrastructure of any urban area in Nepal, और its economy is केन्द्रित on पर्यटन, जिससे accounted for 3.8 % of नेपाल 's जीडीपी in 1995–96.
( Tourism in काठमांडू declined thereafter दौरान a period of राजनैतिक unrest, लकिन since तब रै improved. )
The city has a समृद्ध इतिहास, spanning nearly 2000 सालो, as inferred from inscriptions मिला in the घाटी.
Religious and सांस्कृतिक festivities form a प्रमुख part of the जीवनदान of people residing in काठमांडू.
सबसे of काठमांडू 's people follow हिंदुत्व और अनेक अन्य follow buddhism.
वहीँ are लोगों of अन्य religious beliefs as well, giving काठमांडू a कॉस्मोपॉलिटन संस्कृति.
नेपाली is the सबसे commonly बोला भाषा in the city.
Nepal bhasa is the indigenous भाषा spoken by the नेवार लोगों.
Hindi is widely understood और अंग्रेज़ी is understood by काठमांडू 's educated निवासियों.
The city 's literacy rate is 98 %.
काठमांडू 's सिस्टर शहरों ( ललितपुर patan ) and भक्तपुर हैं अभिन्न to Kathmandu 's सांस्कृतिक heritage, पर्यटन industry, और economy ; therefore UNESCO 's संसार विरासत साईट सूचियाँ all तीन cities ' monuments and आकर्षण साथ अंतर्गत एक heading, `` काठमांडू Valley- युनेस्को संसार Heritage साईट ``.
फ़ील्ड हॉकी, usually referred to simply as हॉकी, is a टोली खेल of the हॉकी परिवार जिससे is निभाई between दो teams of eleven खिलाड़ी with हॉकी sticks और a मुश्किल, solid plastic बॉल.
at the turn of the 21st सदी, the game is played globally, साथ particular popularity throughout यूरोपीय, Asia, महासागरीय, और South America – in जोड to होने the national खेल of Pakistan और India.
the पद `` field हॉकी '' is used primarily in कनाडा, the United राज्य, and other regions of the world जहाँ the sport of बर्फ हॉकी is अधिक लोकप्रिय.
दौरान खेल, लक्ष्य keepers हैं the तभी खिलाड़ी who हैं अनुमत to touch the बॉल with कोई भाग of their देह ( साथ the एक्सेप्शन of a player 's hand considered 'part of the स्टिक ' ), with this तभी applying भीतर the shooting वृत्त ( भी ज्ञात as the D, or शूटिंग चाप, or just the वृत्त ), जबकि field players खेल the बॉल with the flat side of उनके स्टिक.
The team कि स्कोर the सबसे लक्ष्य by the समाप्त of the match विन्स.
if the score is tied at the समाप्त of the खेल, either a draw is घोषित or the game goes into अतिरिक्त समय and/or a penalty shootout, depending on the प्रतियोगिता 's format.
The शासी body of हॉकी is the अंतरराष्ट्रीय हॉकी संघ ( fih ), with men और women होने represented internationally in competitions सहित the Olympic games, राष्ट्रमंडल games, Hockey World Cup, Champions ट्रॉफी और जूनियर हॉकी संसार कप, with many countries कार्यशील extensive junior, senior, and masters ' क्लबों प्रतियोगिताओं.

a लोकप्रिय रूपांतर of field हॉकी is indoor हॉकी, जिससे differs in a number of respects जबकि मूर्त the primary principles of हॉकी.

the संसार Wide Web ( abbreviated as WWW or w3, commonly ज्ञात as the वेब ), is a प्रणाली of interlinked hypertext documents पहुँचा via the अंतरजाल.
साथ a web browser, एक can view web पृष्ठों कि may contain text, बिंब, videos, और अन्य multimedia, और navigate between उन्हें via hyperlinks.
using अवधारणाओं इससे उसके पहले hypertext प्रणालियों जैसे enquire, अंग्रेजों इंजीनियर, कंप्यूटर वैज्ञानिक and at कि समय employee of the cern, Sir Tim Berners-Lee, now निदेशक of the World चौड़ी वेब consortium ( w3c ), लिखा a प्रस्ताव in March 1989 लिये कया होता आखिरकार become the संसार चौड़ी Web.
at cern, a European research संगठन निकट जेनेवा straddling the किनारा between France और स्विट्ज़रलैंड, Berners-Lee और belgian कंप्यूटर scientist रॉबर्ट Cailliau proposed in 1990 to use hypertext `` to कड़ी और अभिगम सूचना of various kinds as a वेब of नोड in which the user can browse at होगा '', और they publicly introduced the प्रोजेक्ट in दिसम्बर of the same year.

a sump पंप is a पंप प्रयुक्त to remove water that has संचित in a जल collecting sump basin, commonly found in the तहखाने of homes.
The water may enter via the घेरा नालों of a basement waterproofing प्रणाली, funneling into the जलाशय or क्युकी of rain or natural ground जल, if the तहखाने is नीचे the जल table स्तर.
sump पंपों हैं प्रयुक्त जहाँ basement flooding happens regularly and to उपाय dampness जहाँ the जल table is ऊपर the न्यास of a home.
sump पंपों भेजें water दूर from a हाउस to कोई place जहाँ it is no longer problematic, such as a नगरपालिका तूफ़ान drain or a dry खूब.
पंपों may discharge to the sanitary sewer in older संस्थापना.
एकबार considered acceptable, this अभ्यास may अभी violate the plumbing कोड or नगरपालिका bylaws, क्युकी it can overwhelm the municipal मलजल treatment प्रणाली.
Municipalities urge homeowners to डिस्कनेक्ट और reroute sump पंप निर्वहन दूर इससे sanitary sewers.
Fines may be imposed for noncompliance.
अनेक homeowners have inherited उनके sump pump configurations and do नहीं एहसास कि the pump discharges to the sewer.
if the निर्वहन is fed to a laundry डूबना in the तहखाने, it 's संभावित going to the सीवर.
प्रायः hardwired into a home 's विद्युत प्रणाली, sump पंपों may have a battery backup.
the घर 's pressurized जल सप्लाई powers कुछ पंपों, eliminating the need लिये विद्युत at the व्यय of using potable जल, potentially बनाना उन्हें अधिक expensive to operate than विद्युत पंपों and creating an additional जल disposal problem.
चूंकि a sump जलाशय may अतिप्रवाह if नहीं constantly उत्तेजित, a बैकअप प्रणाली is महत्वपूर्ण for मामले जब the प्रमुख शक्ति is out लिये prolonged अवधि of time, as during a कठोर तूफ़ान.
वहीँ हैं generally दो प्रकार of sump पंपों — pedestal and submersible.
The pedestal pump 's मोटर is mounted above the sump, जहाँ it is more easily सर्विस, लकिन is भी अधिक conspicuous.
the pump impeller is चलित by a long, लंबवत एक्सटेंशन शाफ्ट और the impeller is in a स्क्रॉल आवास in the base of the पंप.
The submersible pump is entirely आरोहित inside the sump, और is specially sealed to prevent electrical छोटी circuits.
sump पंप प्रणालियों हैं भी utilized in industrial और commercial अनुप्रयोग to control जल तालिका -सुनानाd समस्याएं in surface soil.
an आर्टेसियन aquifer or आवधिक high जल तालिका हालात can cause the मैदान to become अस्थिर due to जल संतृप्त.
as long as the पंप functions, the सतह मृदा will remain stable.
ये sumps हैं typically ten feet in depth or अधिक ; lined साथ corrugated metal पाइप that contains perforations or नाली holes throughout.
They may शामिल electronic control प्रणालियों with विज़ुअल और audible सचेतक and are usually covered to prevent debris and पशु from गिरना in.
bleeding कान्सास, खूनी Kansas or the Border युद्ध, थी a series of हिंसक political confrontations involving anti-slavery free-staters and pro-slavery `` Border ruffian `` तत्व, that took प्लेस in the कान्सास Territory और the neighboring towns of मिसौरी between 1854 और 1861.
At the दिल of the conflict was the question of whether कान्सास would डालें the Union as a फ़्री state or स्लेव राज्य.
as ऐसे, Bleeding Kansas was a प्रॉक्सी युद्ध between northerners और Southerners over the समस्या of slavery in the United राज्य.
the term `` Bleeding Kansas '' थी coined by होरेस greeley of the नई York Tribune ; the events it encompasses सीधे presaged the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध.
कॉंग्रेस had long struggled to संतुलन the interests of pro-slavery forces और anti-slavery शक्तियां.
The events बाद known as bleeding Kansas were नियत into गति by the Kansas–Nebraska Act of 1854, जिससे nullified the मिसौरी सुलह और बजाय implemented the concept of लोकप्रिय sovereignty.
an ostensibly लोकतांत्रिक विचार, popular प्रभुता stated कि the निवासियों of each territory or state चाहिए decide whether it would be a free or स्लेव राज्य ; however, this resulted in immigration en masse to Kansas by activists इससे both sides.
at एक पाइंट, कान्सास था two पृथक सरकारें, प्रत्येक साथ इसके own संविधान, हालांकि तभी एक was federally पहचाना.
on जनवरी 29, 1861, कान्सास was admitted to the Union as a free राज्य, कम than three months पहले the बैटल of Fort sumter जिससे began the सिविल युद्ध.
बेंजीन is an सशुल्क रासायनिक यौगिक साथ the आणविक सूत्र c6 H|Hydrogen|H6.
Its molecule is रचित of 6 carbon अणु joined in a ring, with 1 hydrogen अणु संलग्न to each carbon atom.
Because इसके अणुओं contain तभी कार्बन और हाइड्रोजन atoms, बेंजीन is classed as a हाइड्रोकार्बन.
बेंजीन is a natural constituent of crude आयल, और is एक of the सबसे मौलिक petrochemicals.
Benzene is an खुशबूदार हाइड्रोकार्बन and the second [ n ] - annulene ( [ 6 ] -annulene ), a चक्रीय hydrocarbon साथ a निरन्तर pi बंध.
It is sometimes abbreviated ph –h. Benzene is a colorless and highly flammable liquid साथ a मीठी महकते.
It is मुख्यतः प्रयुक्त as a precursor to भारी chemicals, such as ethylbenzene और cumene, which are produced on a billion किलोग्राम स्केल.
क्युकी it has a ऊँची ऑक्टेन क्रमांक, it is an important component of गैसोलीन, composing a few प्रतिशत of इसके द्रव्यमान.
सबसे non-industrial अनुप्रयोग have महरूम सीमित by benzene 's carcinogenicity.

In more सामान्य terms, Wii Homebrew refers to the उपयोग of the Wii 's हार्डवेयर, accessories और तन्त्र लिये उद्देश्य outside those intended by the निर्माता.

if there are मतभेद between the निषेचित संयंत्र group and the unfertilized `` कंट्रोल '' समूह, ये differences may be due to the उर्वरक.
A scientific कंट्रोल is an प्रयोग or अवलोकन designed to minimize the effects of परिवर्तनीय अन्य than the single स्वतंत्र variable.
This increases the विश्वसनीयता of the परिणाम, often through a comparison between कंट्रोल measurements और the अन्य माप.
वैज्ञानिक controls हैं a part of the scientific विधि.
For उदाहरण, दौरान ड्रग testing, scientists होगा कोशिश to कंट्रोल दो groups to रखना them as identical as possible, तब allow एक group to कोशिश the ड्रग.
another उदाहरण might be testing संयंत्र fertilizer by giving it to only हाफ the पौधे in a गार्डन : the पौधे that receive no उर्वरक हैं the control समूह, क्युकी वे establish the बेसलाइन स्तर of growth कि the fertilizer-treated पौधे होगा be compared against.
बगैर a कंट्रोल समूह, the प्रयोग can not determine whether the fertilizer-treated plants grow अधिक than वे होता have if untreated.
Ideally, सब परिवर्तनीय in an experiment होगा be controlled ( accounted लिये by the कंट्रोल measurements ) and none होगा be uncontrolled.
In such an प्रयोग, if सब the नियंत्रण कार्य as अपेक्षित, it is संभावित to conclude that the प्रयोग is working as intended और that the परिणाम of the experiment हैं due to the effect of the परिवर्तनीय being tested.
कि is, वैज्ञानिक नियंत्रण allow an investigator to make a अर्जी जैसे `` Two परिस्थितियों यहूद identical until factor x occurred.
Since फ़ैक्टर X is the only difference between the दो परिस्थितियों, the new निष्कर्ष was caused by फ़ैक्टर x. ''

जॉन एडम्स ( October 30, 1735 ( o.s. अक्तूबर 19, 1735 ) – जुलाई 4, 1826 ) was the second अध्यक्ष of the United States ( 1797–1801 ), having पहले परोसा as the first vice अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य.
An अमरीकी founding Father, he थी a statesman, diplomat, और a leading advocate of अमरीकी स्वतंत्रता इससे Great Britain.
खूब शिक्षित, he थी an Enlightenment political theorist who प्रचारित republicanism और लिखा prolifically about उसके प्रायः seminal विचार, both in प्रकाशित works and in letters to his बीवी और कुंजी adviser अबीगैल as well as to other founding Fathers.
एडम्स आए to prominence in the जल्दी stages of the अमरीकी क्रान्ति.
A lawyer और पब्लिक figure in बोस्टन, as a प्रतिनिधि इससे मैसाचुसेट्स to the महाद्वीपीय Congress, he निभाई a leading भूमिका in persuading कॉंग्रेस to घोषित स्वतंत्रता.
he assisted थामस जेफरसन in drafting the Declaration of Independence in 1776, और थी इसके प्राथमिक एडवोकेट in the कॉंग्रेस.
Later, as a राजनयिक in यूरोपीय, he helped negotiate the eventual सलाम सन्धि साथ Great Britain, और was responsible लिये obtaining vital governmental लोन from Amsterdam बैंकर्स.
A राजनैतिक theorist and इतिहासकार, एडम्स largely wrote the Massachusetts Constitution in 1780, which साथ साथ उसके earlier विचार on सरकारी, बहकावे American राजनैतिक विचार.
One of उसके महानतम roles थी as a न्यायधीश of character : in 1775, he मनोनीत जार्ज वॉशिंगटन to be commander-in-chief, और 25 years बाद nominated John मार्शल to be Chief Justice of the संयुक्त राज्य.
Adams ' revolutionary credentials secured उसे दो terms as जार्ज Washington 's vice अध्यक्ष and उसके own चुनाव in 1796 as the दूसरी president.
दौरान his एक term, he encountered ferocious हमले by the jeffersonian republicans, as खूब as the प्रबल faction in his अपना Federalist Party led by उसके bitter दुश्मन सिकंदर हैमिल्टन.
एडम्स signed the विवादास्पद Alien and राजद्रोह Acts, और built up the फौज और नेवी especially in the फेस of an undeclared नवल युद्ध ( पुकारा the `` Quasi-War `` ) साथ फ़्रांस, 1798–1800.
The प्रमुख accomplishment of his presidency थी his शांतिपूर्ण resolution of the विरोध in the फेस of हैमिल्टन 's विपक्ष.
in 1800, एडम्स थी defeated for re-election by Thomas जेफरसन और रिटायर्ड to मैसाचुसेट्स.
He later resumed his friendship with जेफरसन.
he and उसके wife, अबीगैल एडम्स, founded an संपन्नता परिवार line of राजनेता, राजनयिकों, और इतिहासकारों अभी referred to as the एडम्स political परिवार.
एडम्स थी the पिता of John Quincy एडम्स, the छठे अध्यक्ष of the United States.
उसके achievements have received greater मान्यता in modern times, हालांकि his योगदान were नहीं initially as मनाये as those of अन्य Founders.
एडम्स थी the पहला U.S. अध्यक्ष to reside in the भवन that आखिरकार became ज्ञात as the श्वेत हाउस.
a Watt भाप engine.
the steam इंजन, fuelled primarily by कोयले, propelled the औद्योगिक Revolution in Great ब्रिटेन और the world.
the Industrial क्रान्ति थी the परिवर्तन to नई manufacturing प्रक्रियाओं that occurred in the period इससे परिचय 1760 to some समय between 1820 and 1840.
इस परिवर्तन included going from हाथ production methods to मशीने, नई रासायनिक निर्माण और आयरन उत्पादन प्रक्रियाओं, improved दक्षता of जल शक्ति, the increasing use of steam शक्ति and विकास of यंत्र tools.
The परिवर्तन भी शामिल the change इससे wood और other bio-fuels to कोयले.
the औद्योगिक revolution began in Britain and भीतर a few दशकों spread to पश्चिमी यूरोपीय and the United राज्य.
the Industrial क्रान्ति marks a प्रमुख turning पाइंट in इतिहास ; लगभग प्रत्येक aspect of daily जीवन थी बहकावे in कुछ way.
सबसे notably, औसत आय और जनसांख्यिकी began to प्रदर्शनी unprecedented sustained विकास.
in the शब्द of Nobel Prize विजेता रॉबर्ट E. लुकास, Jr., `` लिये the first समय in इतिहास, the living standards of the masses of ordinary लोगों have begun to undergo sustained विकास... nothing remotely जैसे this आर्थिक बर्ताव is उल्लेखित by the classical अर्थशास्त्रियों, even as a theoretical सम्भावना. ''
William घंटी स्कॉट आयरन और Coal, 1855-60
The period of समय covered by the औद्योगिक क्रान्ति varies साथ अलग इतिहासकारों.
eric hobsbawm आयोजित that it 'broke आउट ' in Britain in the 1780s and थी not fully felt जबतक the 1830s or 1840s, जबकि T. S. एश्टन आयोजित कि it occurred roughly between 1760 और 1830.
कुछ 20th-century historians such as जॉन clapham और Nicholas Crafts have argued कि the process of आर्थिक and सोशल बदलें took place धीरे और the पद क्रान्ति is a misnomer.
This is स्टिल a विषय of बहस among historians.
जीडीपी per capita थी broadly stable पहले the औद्योगिक क्रान्ति and the emergence of the modern पूंजीवादी economy.
the औद्योगिक Revolution began an era of per-capita economic विकास in पूंजीवादी economies.
आर्थिक historians are in अनुबंध कि the onset of the औद्योगिक क्रान्ति is the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण event in the इतिहास of मानवता चूंकि the domestication of पशु and plants.
the पहला Industrial क्रान्ति evolved into the Second औद्योगिक Revolution in the transition years between 1840 और 1870, जब technological और आर्थिक प्रगति gained momentum साथ the increasing अपनाना of steam-powered boats, जहाजों और रेल, the विशाल स्केल manufacture of machine tools and the increasing use of steam संचालित factories.

the विशाल intestine ( or bowel, colon ) is the पिछला भाग of the digestive system in vertebrate animals.
इसके function is to absorb water इससे the remaining indigestible खाना पदार्थ, और तब to pass व्यर्थ बर्बाद सामग्री इससे the देह.
This आलेख is primarily परिचय the इंसान gut, हालांकि the information about इसके प्रक्रियाओं are directly applicable to सबसे mammals.
the विशाल intestine consists of the cecum, rectum and anal canal.
It starts in the सही iliac region of the pelvis, बस at or नीचे the सही waist, जहाँ it is joined to the नीचे समाप्त of the small आंत.
From यहाँ it continues up the उदर, तब आरपार the चौडाई of the abdominal गुहा, और तब it turns down, continuing to इसके endpoint at the anus.
the विशाल intestine is परिचय long, जिससे is परिचय one-fifth of the पूरे लंबाई of the intestinal कनाल.
in terminologia Anatomica the large intestine शामिल the cecum, कोलन, मलाशय, and गुदा कनाल.
However, कुछ sources exclude the anal canal.
The ग्रीन Bay पैकर्स हैं an American football टोली आधारित in Green Bay, विस्कॉन्सिन.
They हैं सदस्यों of the उत्तर Division of the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल Conference ( NFC ) in the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल League ( NFL ).
Green खाड़ी is the third-oldest franchise in the NFL, having been organized और playing in 1919.
the पैकर्स हैं the only non-profit, community-owned major लीग पेशेवर sports टोली in the United States.
The Packers हैं the last vestige of `` small कस्बा टीमों '' कि were once common in the NFL दौरान the 1920s और 1930s.
Founded in 1919 by Earl `` घुंघराले '' lambeau ( hence the name lambeau फ़ील्ड on जिससे the टोली plays ) और जार्ज Whitney calhoun, the ग्रीन Bay पैकर्स can ट्रेस their lineage to other semi-professional टीमों in ग्रीन खाड़ी डेटिंग back to 1896.
In 1919 और 1920 the Packers competed as a semi-professional football team against clubs इससे around विस्कॉन्सिन और the मिडवेस्ट.
वे joined the अमरीकी पेशेवर Football संघ ( apfa ) in 1921, the forerunner to कया is known today as the National फ़ुटबॉल लीग ( NFL ).
हालांकि Green खाड़ी is the last NFL `` छोटी कस्बा '' टोली, इसके local fan आधार and मीडिया extends into nearby मिल्वौकी ; the team भी played selected घर games there between 1933 और 1994.
The Green खाड़ी पैकर्स have won 13 लीग championships ( अधिक than कोई अन्य team in the एनएफएल ), including नौ एनएफएल championships prior to the सुपर Bowl era और चार सुपर Bowl victories —in 1967 ( सुपर Bowl i ), 1968 ( सुपर Bowl ii ), 1997 ( सुपर कटोरी XXXI ) और 2011 ( सुपर Bowl xlv ).
the Packers have long-standing, bitter rivalries साथ उनके nfc उत्तर ( formerly the NFC सेंट्रल ) opponents, the शिकागो bears, मिनेसोटा वाइकिंग्स and the डेट्रॉयट शेर.
the bears-packers rivalry is एक of the oldest rivalries in एनएफएल history, dating वापस to 1921.

Mount mckinley ( also ज्ञात as Denali लिया इससे the इनुइट Koyukon athabaskan भाषा meaning `` The ग्रेट One '' ) is the उच्चतम पहाड़ peak in the United राज्य and in उत्तर America साथ a summit elevation of ऊपर समुद्र स्तर.
at कुछ, the आधार to peak वृद्धि is माना the largest of any पहाड़ situated entirely ऊपर sea स्तर.
measured by topographic prominence, it is the तीसरा सबसे prominent peak after माउंट एवरेस्ट and अकोंकागुआ.
स्तिथ in the अलास्का दायरा in the आंतरिक of US state of Alaska, it is the centerpiece of Denali नेशनल पार्क और बचाना.
The पहला यूरोपीय to दस्तावेज़ sighting the पहाड़ थी जार्ज Vancouver in 1794.
In 1903, James wickersham अंकित the पहला attempt at climbing McKinley which was unsuccessful.
In 1906, Frederick कुक claimed the पहला ascent जिससे was बाद सिद्ध to be गलत.
The first verifiable ascent to mckinley 's summit थी हासिल on जून 7, 1913 by चढना Hudson stuck, हैरी karstens, वाल्टर हार्पर, और रॉबर्ट टैटम.
in 1951, Bradford washburn pioneered the West buttress रूट considered to be the safest और easiest रूट and इसलिए the most लोकप्रिय currently in उपयोग.
the होंडा S600 is an automobile manufactured by होंडा.
It थी शुभारम्भ in कूच 1964.
उपलब्धियाँ as a roadster – bearing दमदार resemblance to the Honda s500 – and as a fastback coupé – introduced in कूच 1965 – the s600 थी the पहला होंडा उपलब्धियाँ in दो trim स्तर.
दौरान इसके उत्पादन चलाएं up to 1966, the मॉडल स्टाइलिंग होता remain pretty much the वही, with the most notable changes coming to the सामने grille, बम्पर, and headlights.
Powered by a dohc, water-cooled, four-cylinder इनलाइन इंजन with four carburetors, the इंजन क्षमता थी increased to 606 cc इससे the s500 's 531 cc.
The engine उत्पादित at 8,500 आरपीएम और था a top speed of.

The S600 was the पहला mass marketed होंडा car.

बियोवुल्फ़ ( ; in Old अंग्रेज़ी or ) is the conventional शीर्षक of an बूढ़ा English वीर epic कविता consisting of 3182 alliterative long लाइनों, नियत in Scandinavia, commonly cited as एक of the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण works of anglo-saxon साहित्य.
It survives in a single पाण्डुलिपि ज्ञात as the Nowell codex.
इसके composition by an बेनाम anglo-saxon poet is दिनाँक between the 8th और the जल्दी 11th century.
in 1731, the पाण्डुलिपि was badly क्षतिग्रस्त by a fire कि swept through a भवन आवास a संग्रहण of मध्यकालीन manuscripts समवेत by Sir Robert Bruce Cotton.
the कविता गिरी into obscurity लिये दशकों, and its अस्तित्व did नहीं become widely ज्ञात again जबतक it was मुद्रित in 1815 in an संस्करण prepared by the Icelandic-Danish विद्वान grímur jónsson Thorkelin.
In the कविता, बियोवुल्फ़, a hero of the Geats in scandinavia, आता to the help of hroðgar, the king of the Danes, whose mead हॉल ( in Heorot ) रै been अंतर्गत आक्रमण by a monster ज्ञात as grendel.
बाद बियोवुल्फ़ जानबूझ उसे, Grendel 's mother attacks the hall और is तब also defeated.
Victorious, बियोवुल्फ़ goes घर to geatland in Sweden और later becomes king of the geats.
After a काल of fifty सालो has passed, बियोवुल्फ़ defeats a ड्रैगन, but is fatally wounded in the बैटल.
बाद उसके death, his सेवकों दफनाने उसे in a tumulus, a दफ़न mound, in Geatland.
Shem हैम और japheth by James Tissot 1904.
shem ( ; Sēm ; अरबी : sām ; Ge'ez : ሴም, sēm ; `` renown ; समृद्धि ; नाम '' ) थी one of the बेटे of Noah in the Hebrew Bible as खूब as in Islamic literature.
he is सबसे popularly regarded as the ज्येष्ठ son, though कुछ traditions लिहाज़ him as the दूसरी son.
Genesis 10:21 refers to relative आयु of Shem और his brother Japheth, लकिन साथ sufficient ambiguity to have yielded different अनुवाद.
the श्लोक is अनूदित in the kjv as `` Unto Shem भी, the father of सब the children of eber, the bhai of japheth the elder, even to उसे were children born. ``.
However, the New American मानक बाइबल देता, `` भी to shem, the पिता of सब the children of eber, और the older bhai of japheth, children were born. ''
Genesis 11:10 रिकॉर्ड कि shem थी still 100 सालो बूढ़ा at the birth of arphaxad, ( लकिन nearly 101 - देखिए Chronology नोट, ) दो सालो बाद the flood, बनाना उसे मुश्किल 99 at the समय the flood began ; और कि he जिया लिये another 500 सालो बाद this, बनाना his आयु at death 600 सालो.
the children of Shem यहूद ईलम, asshur, arphaxad, lud, और aram, in जोड to बेटियां.
Abraham, the patriarch of the Hebrews और arabs, थी एक of the descendants of arphaxad.
इस्लामी literature describes shem as एक of the believing बेटे of नूह.
Some स्त्रोत भी पहचानो shem as a prophet in his own right और कि he थी the अगला prophet बाद उसके पिता.
in एक मुस्लिम लेजेंड, shem थी one of the लोगों that God बना यीशु उठाएगा as a चिह्न to the children of Israel.
the 1st सदी इतिहासकार Flavius josephus, among अनेक अन्य, recounted the परंपरा कि ये पाँच बेटे यहूद the progenitors of the nations of ईलम, Assyria, chaldea, लीडिया, and सीरियाई, respectively.
सामीती is still a commonly used पद for the Semitic languages, as a उपसमुच्चय of the afro-asiatic languages, denoting the आम linguistic heritage of Arabic, Aramaic, अक्कादी, ethiopic, Hebrew and Phoenician भाषाएं.
According to कुछ यहूदी traditions ( e.g., B. talmud nedarim 32b ; Genesis rabbah 46:7 ; Genesis rabbah 56:10 ; leviticus Rabbah 25:6 ; Numbers rabbah 4:8. ), shem is believed to have been Melchizedek, किंग of सलेम whom अब्राहम is recorded to have met after the battle of the चार किंग्स.
In a few of the अनेक extra-biblical sources that describe उसे, shem is भी credited साथ killing nimrod, बेटे of Cush.
Shem is उल्लेखित in उत्पत्ति 5:32, 6:10 ; 7:13 ; 9:18,23,26-27 ; 10 ; 11:10 ; भी in 1 Chronicles 1:4.
भौगोलिक identifications of flavius josephus, c. 100 ad ; japheth 's sons दिखाया in रेड, Ham 's बेटे in ब्लू, shem 's बेटे in green.

अंडोरा ( ;, ), officially the Principality of अंडोरा ( ), भी called the principality of the घाटियों of Andorra, ( ), is a landlocked microstate in Southwestern यूरोपीय, located in the पूर्वी Pyrenees kyu और bordered by स्पेन और फ़्रांस.
it is the छठे smallest स्वदेश in यूरोपीय, having an क्षेत्रफल of and an estimated जनसांख्यिकी of 85,000 in 2012.
इसके capital, Andorra la वेला, is the highest पूंजी नगर in Europe, at an उन्नयन of above समुद्र level.
the आधिकारिक language is कैटलन, although स्पेनी, Portuguese, and French are भी commonly बोला.
Created under a चार्टर in 988, the present principality was formed in 1278.
it is known as a principality as it is a साम्राज्य headed by दो co-princes – the बिशप of urgell and the अध्यक्ष of France.
Andorra is a prosperous country मुख्यतः क्युकी of इसके पर्यटन industry, जिससे services an अनुमानित 10.2 million visitors annually, and भी क्युकी of इसके status as a tax हेवन.
It is नहीं a सदस्य of the European संघ, लकिन the euro is the de facto करेंसी.
The लोगों of Andorra have the 4th उच्चतम इंसान जीवन expectancy in the संसार — 82 years at जनम.

Oahu ( ) or oahu, known as `` the महफ़िल प्लेस '', is the तीसरा largest of the हवाई आइलैंड्स और the most populous of the आइलैंड्स in the u.S. राज्य of हवाई.
The state पूंजी, होनोलूलू, is on oahu 's southeast coast.
Including छोटी close-in offshore islands such as Ford द्वीप and the islands in Kaneohe Bay और बंद the eastern ( windward ) coast, it रै a total land area of, बनाना it the 20th largest island in the United States.
in the महानतम आयाम, इस volcanic island is long और across.

Spelt, भी known as dinkel गेहूं, or hulled wheat, is an ancient species of wheat from the पांचवां millennium bc.
Spelt थी an महत्वपूर्ण स्टेपल in भाग of यूरोपीय from the Bronze Age to मध्यकालीन टाइम्स ; it now survives as a relict क्रॉप in Central यूरोपीय और उत्तरी स्पेन and रै found a नई मार्केट as a स्वास्थ्य खाना.

it is a hexaploid गेहूं, which अर्थात् it has छह सेट of गुणसूत्रों.
शर्लक Holmes ( or ) is a fictional detective निर्मित by लेखक and चिकित्सक सर Arthur कोनन डोयल.
a london-based `` परामर्श जासूस '' whose abilities border on the fantastic, holmes is प्रसिद्ध for उसके astute logical तर्क, his ability to अपनाना लगभग कोई disguise, और उसके use of forensic science कौशल to solve difficult मामले.
Holmes, who पहला appeared in publication in 1887, थी प्रदर्शित in four novels and 56 short stories.
The first अनोखा, a पढ़ाई in स्कारलेट, appeared in Beeton 's क्रिसमस सालाना in 1887 और the दूसरी, The चिह्न of the Four, in lippincott 's Monthly Magazine in 1890.
the अक्षर grew tremendously in popularity with the first श्रेणी of छोटी कहानियां in the Strand पत्रिका, शुरूआत साथ a Scandal in Bohemia in 1891 ; further series of छोटी कहानियां and two novels प्रकाशित in serial रूप appeared between then and 1927.
the कहानियां कवर a period from around 1880 up to 1914.
All लकिन चार कहानियां हैं narrated by holmes 's dost और biographer, dr. जॉन H. वाटसन ; दो हैं narrated by holmes खुद ( `` the Blanched Soldier `` and `` The शेर 's माने `` ) और two अन्य हैं लिखा in the तीसरा person ( `` The Mazarin स्टोन `` and `` His Last धनुष `` ).
In दो कहानियां ( `` the musgrave Ritual `` और `` the ग्लोरिया स्कॉट `` ), holmes tells Watson the प्रमुख story इससे उसके memories, while वाटसन becomes the narrator of the frame स्टोरी.
The first और चौथी novels, a Study in स्कारलेट और the Valley of भय, प्रत्येक include a long interval of omniscient narration recounting events अनजान to either holmes or वाटसन.
the संयुक्त राज्य हाउस of Representatives is एक of the two घरों of the संयुक्त States कॉंग्रेस ( a bicameral विधानमंडल ).
it is अक्सर referred to as the हाउस.
the अन्य हाउस is the सीनेट.
the संयोजन और शक्तियां of the हाउस हैं स्थापित in Article एक of the United States Constitution.
The प्रमुख शक्ति of the House is to pass federal विधान कि affects the entire country although इसके bills must भी be passed by the सीनेट and further सहमत to by the u.S. President पहले बनने विधि ( unless दोनो the House और सीनेट re-pass the legislation साथ a two-thirds बहुमत in प्रत्येक कक्ष ).
the हाउस has several exclusive powers : the power to initiate आय bills, to impeach officials, और to elect the U.S. अध्यक्ष in मामला there is no majority in the Electoral College.
Each u.S. राज्य is represented in the हाउस in proportion to इसके population but is हकदार to at तनिक एक प्रतिनिधि.
The सबसे populous state, California, फिलहाल रै 53 प्रतिनिधि.
The कुल क्रमांक of मतदान प्रतिनिधि is फिक्स्ड by विधि at 435.
Each प्रतिनिधि serves लिये a two-year पद.
the स्पीकर of the United States House of Representatives, who presides over the chamber, is elected by the members of the House, और is इसलिए traditionally the leader of the हाउस लोकतांत्रिक caucus or the House Republican सम्मेलन, whichever party has more मतदान सदस्यों.
the House meets in the south wing of the संयुक्त States Capitol.

kennywood is an मनोरंजन park स्तिथ in West mifflin, Pennsylvania, a उपनगरीय of पिट्सबर्ग.
the park पहला खोली in 1898 as a `` ट्राली park '' आकर्षण at the समाप्त of the mellon परिवार 's monongahela गली रेल.
The पार्क थी खरीदा in 1906 by F. W. Henninger और एंड्रयू McSwigan and thus began the Kennywood Entertainment कम्पनी that रै remained a closely आयोजित परिवार कारोबार लिये over 100 सालो.
इस traditional amusement park still रै structures and rides dating back to इसके opening and the जल्दी 1900s.
साथ with Rye playland पार्क, it is एक of only two amusement parks सूचीबद्ध in the नेशनल पंजीकरण of ऐतिहासिक Places.

Minimalism describes आंदोलनों in various फ़ॉर्म of आर्ट और डिज़ाइन, विशेषकर visual आर्ट and म्यूज़िक, जहाँ the work is नियत आउट to expose the essence or पहचान of a विषय through eliminating all non-essential फ़ॉर्म, सुविधाएँ or अवधारणाओं.
Minimalism is any design or style in जिससे the simplest and fewest elements are प्रयुक्त to बनाएँ the अधिकतम प्रभाव.
as a विशिष्ट गति in the कला it is identified with developments in post–world War II पश्चिमी Art, सबसे strongly साथ American विज़ुअल arts in the 1960s and जल्दी 1970s.
prominent artists associated साथ इस गति include डोनाल्ड judd, John mccracken, agnes मार्टिन, डान flavin, रॉबर्ट मॉरिस, ऐनी truitt, और फ़्रैंक Stella.

the शर्तें have expanded to encompass a movement in म्यूज़िक जिससे सुविधाएँ repetition और iteration, as in the रचनाएं of La मोंटे Young, टेरी रिले, स्टीव Reich, फिलिप Glass, और John Adams.

it has भी been used to describe the plays और novels of सैमुएल Beckett, the films of रॉबर्ट bresson, the कहानियां of रेमंड carver, और even the ऑटोमोबाइल डिजाइन of कोलिन chapman.

इस empirical विधि was observed by John डाल्टन in 1801 and is सम्बन्धित to the आदर्श gas कानून.

the मुख्य इंसाफ of the United राज्य is the head of the United राज्य federal court system ( the न्यायिक शाखा of the federal सरकारी of the संयुक्त राज्य ) और the chief न्यायधीश of the परम् अदालत of the United राज्य.
the Chief Justice is एक of nine Supreme अदालत justices ; the other आठ हैं the संबद्ध justices of the परम् अदालत of the United States.
From 1789 जबतक 1866, the दफ्तर was ज्ञात as the Chief इंसाफ of the Supreme Court.
The मुख्य Justice is the उच्चतम न्यायिक अधिकारी in the देश, और अधिनियमों as a मुख्य प्रशासनिक officer लिये the संघीय courts and as सिर of the न्यायिक सम्मेलन of the United राज्य appoints the director of the प्रशासनिक दफ्तर of the United राज्य न्यायालयों.
the Chief Justice also serves as a spokesperson लिये the न्यायिक शाखा.
the मुख्य इंसाफ लीड the business of the परम् Court.
he presides over oral arguments before the अदालत.
जब the अदालत renders an opinion, the Chief Justice—when in the majority—decides जो writes the अदालत 's opinion.
The मुख्य इंसाफ भी has significant agenda-setting power over the अदालत 's meetings.
in the मामला of an impeachment of a अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States, जिससे रै occurred twice, the मुख्य Justice presides over the trial in the Senate.
in आधुनिक परंपरा, the मुख्य Justice has the ceremonial ड्यूटी of administering the oath of office of the अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States.
the पहला Chief Justice थी जॉन Jay.
the 17th and वर्तमान मुख्य Justice is John G. रॉबर्ट्स, Jr.

Prudhoe खाड़ी आयल फ़ील्ड is a large oil फ़ील्ड on Alaska 's North Slope.
it is the largest आयल field in दोनो the संयुक्त States और in North America, covering and originally containing लगभग of आयल.
the राशि of recoverable आयल in the field is अधिक than double कि of the अगला largest फ़ील्ड in the United राज्य, the East टेक्सास oil field.
the field is संचालित by bp ; partners हैं ExxonMobil and ConocoPhillips Alaska.
Labor unions are legally पहचाना as representatives of workers in अनेक उद्योग in the संयुक्त राज्य.
Their कार्यकलाप today centers on सामूहिक bargaining over wages, लाभ, और working शर्तें लिये उनके सदस्यता, and on representing उनके सदस्यों in disputes with management over उल्लंघनों of अनुबंध प्रावधानों.
Larger संघ also typically engage in lobbying क्रियाएँ and electioneering at the state and संघीय स्तर.
सबसे संघ in America हैं aligned साथ एक of two larger छतरियाँ संगठन : the afl-cio created in 1955, और the बदलें to जीत संघ जिससे विभाजित from the afl-cio in 2005.
दोनो advocate नीतियों and विधान on behalf of workers in the United States और कनाडा, और लो an active role in politics.
The AFL-CIO is विशेषकर चिंतित साथ global trade मुद्दे.
In 2010, the प्रतिशत of workers belonging to a संघ in the United States ( or कुल मजदूर union `` घनत्व '' ) was 11.4 %, compared to 18.4 % in Germany, 27.5 % in Canada, और 70 % in फिनलैंड.
संघ membership in the private सेक्टर has गिरे अंतर्गत 7 % — levels नहीं देखी चूंकि 1932.
संघ allege कि employer-incited विपक्ष रै contributed to इस मनाही in सदस्यता.
The सबसे prominent unions are among public सेक्टर कर्मचारी such as teachers and police.
सदस्यों of संघ हैं disproportionately older, पुरूष और निवासियों of the पूर्वोत्तर, the Midwest, और कैलिफ़ोर्निया.
संघ workers average 10-30 % उच्चतर अदा than non-union in America बाद controlling for individual, जॉब, and labor मार्केट विशेषताएँ.
हालांकि much छोटी compared to उनके शिखर सदस्यता in the 1950s, American संघ remain a prominent राजनैतिक factor, दोनो through mobilization of their अपना memberships और through coalitions साथ like-minded activist संगठन around issues such as immigrant अधिकारों, व्यापार नीति, health परवाह, और जीना wage campaigns.
To fight alleged नियोक्ता anti-union कार्यक्रम, unions हैं currently advocating नई `` कार्ड जाँच `` संघीय legislation that होता आवश्यकता नियोक्ता to सौदेबाजी साथ a union if more than 50 % of workers हस्ताक्षरित forms, or `` cards, '' stating they काश to be represented by कि union.
the वर्तमान कार्यविधि involves waiting 45 to 90 days लिये a federally पर्यवेक्षित secret-ballot employee referendum on the विषय.
The economist जोसेफ stiglitz रै asserted कि, `` दमदार unions have helped to reduce inequality, whereas weaker संघ have made it easier for ceos, sometimes working with मार्केट forces कि they have helped shape, to increase it. ''
The decline in unionization since WWII in the संयुक्त राज्य has महरूम संबद्ध साथ a सुनाया rise in आय और माल असमानता.

A boutique is a छोटी shopping आउटलेट, especially एक कि specializes in elite and fashionable वस्तुएं ऐसे as कपडे and jewelry.
the शब्द is फ्रेंच for `` दूकान '', via Latin from यूनानी ἀποθήκη ( apothēkē ), `` storehouse ''.
The पद entered into रोज English उपयोग in the late 1960s जब, for a ब्रैड काल, लंदन थी the centre of the फ़ैशन व्यापार.
Carnaby गली and the किंग्स सड़क यहूद the focus of much मीडिया attention as घर to the सबसे फैशनेबल boutiques of the era.
Now the East of लंदन रै महरूम regenerated and अधिक Boutiques pop up in फैशनेबल क्षेत्रों, ऐसे as Tower Bridge सड़क.
it can also refer to a specialised कड़ ऐसे as a बुटीक निवेश bank or बुटीक विधि कड़.
The word is प्रायः used to describe a प्रॉपर्टी in the independent section of the hotel मार्केट ( ऐसे as the rockwell in लंदन ) in अनुक्रम to distinguish themselves from larger जंजीरों ( ऐसे as हिल्टन होटल ).
In such मामले the establishments उद्देश्य to convey the idea कि the आपरेशन is elite and अत्यधिक specialised.
In the strictest sense of the शब्द, boutiques होता be one-of-a-kind लकिन more generally बोलना, कुछ जंजीरों can be referred to as boutiques if वे specialize in particular शैलियाँ.
Recently, the term `` बुटीक '' has started होने लागू to normally-mass-market items that हैं either niche or उत्पादित in intentionally छोटी संख्याएँ at बहुत high कीमतें.
इस may be referred to as boutique manufacturing.
For example, पहले the रिलीज of the वी, a समय Magazine आलेख सुझाया कि निन्टेंडो could become a `` बुटीक video-game कम्पनी '', producing games for niche ऑडियंस, बल्कि than trying to compete directly with Microsoft and सोनी.

मनस्ताप ( from the Greek ψυχή `` psyche '', लिये mind/soul, और -ωσις `` -ओएसआईs '', लिये abnormal condition or derangement ) refers to an abnormal condition of the mind, और is a generic psychiatric पद लिये a mental state प्रायः वर्णित as involving a `` घाटा of contact साथ वास्तविकता ``.
लोगों suffering इससे psychosis हैं described as psychotic.
मनस्ताप is given to the अधिक कठोर फ़ॉर्म of psychiatric विकार, दौरान which मति and delusions, सकल उत्तेजना or बेहोशी और impaired इनसाइट may occur.
The पद `` psychosis '' is very व्यापक और can औसत anything from अपेक्षाकृत सामान्य aberrant experiences through to the जटिल और catatonic expressions of schizophrenia and द्विध्रुवी type 1 disorder.
moreover a चौड़ी variety of central बेचैन प्रणाली diseases, इससे दोनो external substances and internal physiologic illness, can produce symptoms of मनस्ताप.
This led अनेक professionals to कह कि मनस्ताप is not specific enough as a निदान पद.
despite इस, `` मनस्ताप '' is generally दिए to noticeable deficits in normal बर्ताव ( ऋणात्मक signs ) and more commonly to विविध types of मति or delusional मान्यताओं ( e.g. grandiosity, delusions of persecution ).
किसी exhibiting बहुत obvious लक्षण may be वर्णित as `` frankly psychotic '', whereas एक exhibiting बहुत हल्का लक्षण could be classified in the श्रेणी of an `` attenuated psychotic risk सिंड्रोम ''.
An excess in dopaminergic signalling is traditionally linked to the positive symptoms of मनस्ताप, especially those of schizophrenia.
इस is विचार to occur through a यांत्रिकी of aberrant salience of पर्यावरणीय stimuli.
अनेक antipsychotic drugs तदनुसार निशाना the dopamine system ; meta-analyses of placebo-controlled ट्रायल of ये drugs, however, दिखाएँ either no significant अंतर between ड्रग और placebo, or a very छोटी effect size, suggesting कि the pathophysiology of मनस्ताप is much more complex than an overactive dopamine प्रणाली.
People experiencing मनस्ताप may प्रदर्शनी कुछ व्यक्तित्व परिवर्तन and thought disorder.
depending on इसके गंभीरता, इस may be accompanied by असामान्य or bizarre behavior, as well as परेशानी with सोशल बातचीत and पुतलियों in carrying out रोज़ life क्रियाएँ.

the बेरोजगारी रेट in the us 1910–1960, साथ the years of the Great अवसाद ( 1929–1939 ) highlighted.
the ग्रेट अवसाद थी a कठोर विश्वव्यापी आर्थिक depression in the decade preceding संसार युद्ध II.
the समय of the Great Depression varied across nations, लकिन in सबसे countries it प्रारंभ in 1930 and lasted जबतक the लेट 1930s or middle 1940s.
It was the longest, सबसे फैली, और deepest depression of the 20th century.
in the 21st सदी, the ग्रेट Depression is commonly used as an उदाहरण of how दूर the संसार 's अर्थव्यवस्था can decline.
the अवसाद originated in the U.S., after the पतन in stock कीमतें that began around September 4, 1929, and became विश्वव्यापी न्यूज with the भण्डार मार्केट क्रैश of अक्तूबर 29, 1929 ( ज्ञात as ब्लैक मंगलवार ).
the Great Depression था devastating प्रभाव in देशों rich and ग़रीब.
Personal आय, tax revenue, profits and prices dropped, while अंतरराष्ट्रीय trade plunged by अधिक than 50 %.
Unemployment in the u.S. रोज़ to 25 %, और in some countries rose as ऊँची as 33 %.
Cities सब around the संसार were hit मुश्किल, especially those निर्भर on heavy उद्योग.
Construction थी virtually halted in many countries.
Farming और ग्रामीण areas suffered as क्रॉप कीमतें गिरी by लगभग 60 %.
facing plummeting माँग साथ few वैकल्पिक स्त्रोत of कार्य, areas dependent on primary सेक्टर उद्योग ऐसे as cash cropping, खनन and लॉगिंग suffered the most.
कुछ economies started to रिकवर by the mid-1930s.
in many countries, the ऋणात्मक effects of the Great Depression lasted जबतक the समाप्त of World युद्ध II.
A असामयिक ventricular संकुचन ( पीवीसी ), भी ज्ञात as a असामयिक ventricular complex, ventricular premature संकुचन ( or जटिल or देवालय ) ( vpc ), ventricular premature ताल ( VPB ), or ventricular extrasystole ( ves ), is a अपेक्षाकृत आम इवेंट जहाँ the धड़कन is initiated by Purkinje मछली in the ventricles बल्कि than by the sinoatrial नोड, the normal heartbeat initiator.
the विद्युत कार्यक्रम of the heart detected by the electrocardiogram allow a पीवीसी to be easily distinguished from a normal heart beat.
a PVC may be perceived as a `` skipped ताल `` or लगा as palpitations in the छाती.
in a सामान्य धड़कन, the ventricles अनुबंध बाद the atria have helped to fill उन्हें by contracting ; in इस way the ventricles can पंप a maximized राशि of रक्त both to the फेफड़े और to the बाकी of the body.
in a पीवीसी, the ventricles contract पहला और before the atria have optimally भर the ventricles साथ blood, जिससे means कि circulation is inefficient.
However, सिंगल ताल पीवीसी arrhythmias do नहीं प्रायः पोज़ a खतरे and can be asymptomatic in स्वस्थ individuals.

The Anti-Counterfeiting व्यापार अनुबंध ( ACTA ), is a multinational सन्धि लिये the purpose of establishing international मानकों लिये intellectual प्रॉपर्टी अधिकारों enforcement.
the agreement aims to स्थापित an अंतरराष्ट्रीय विधिक framework for targeting नकली goods, जेनेरिक दवाइयाँ और copyright infringement on the अंतरजाल, और होता create a नई शासी देह बाहर मौजूदा forums, such as the World व्यापार संगठन, the संसार Intellectual प्रॉपर्टी Organization, or the संयुक्त Nations.
The agreement थी signed in October 2011 by ऑस्ट्रेलिया, Canada, Japan, Morocco, नई Zealand, सिंगापुर, दक्षिण Korea, and the United States.
in 2012, मैक्सिको, the European संघ और 22 countries which are member राज्य of the European संघ हस्ताक्षरित as well.
एक signatory ( जापानी ) रै ratified ( formally स्वीकृत ) the अनुबंध, which would आइये into फ़ोर्स in countries कि ratified it after अनुसमर्थन by six देशों.
Supporters have वर्णित the अनुबंध as a जवाब to `` the increase in global व्यापार of नकली goods और pirated copyright सुरक्षित works ''.
Trades Unions representing मजदूर in the म्यूज़िक, film और tv industries और large intellectual property-based संगठन such as the Motion चित्र संघ of America और Pharmaceutical शोध and निर्माताओं of अमेरिका यहूद active in the सन्धि 's विकास.
प्रतिद्वंद्वियों say the सम्मेलन adversely affects आधारभूत अधिकारों including freedom of expression and गोपनीयता.
acta रै भी महरूम criticised by Doctors बगैर Borders लिये endangering access to medicines in विकासशील देशों.
The secret प्रकृति of negotiations has excluded सिविल समाज समूह, developing countries और the सामान्य public इससे the अनुबंध 's negotiation प्रक्रम और it रै महरूम वर्णित as नीति laundering by critics सहित the Electronic Frontier न्यास और the Entertainment Consumers संघ.
The हस्ताक्षर of the eu और अनेक of its सदस्य राज्य resulted in the resignation in विरोध of the यूरोपीय पार्लियामेंट 's नियुक्त मुख्य investigator, rapporteur कादर आरिफ, as खूब as widespread protests आरपार Europe.
in 2012 the newly-appointed rapporteur, अंग्रेजों mep दाउद Martin, अनुशंसित against the treaty, stating : `` the intended benefits of इस अंतरराष्ट्रीय agreement are far outweighed by the potential खतरे to सिविल लिबर्टीज ''.
On 4 July 2012, the European पार्लियामेंट rejected the agreement in plenary सत्र, साथ 478 मतदान against the सन्धि, 39 in पक्ष और 165 meps abstaining.
FAW semi-trailer truck in China
ट्रैक्टर साथ पक्ष dump ट्रेलर semi-trailer
a ट्रैक्टर साथ an auto-transport semi-trailer.
semi-trailer truck साथ स्लीपर behind the टैक्सी.
A semi-trailer truck is an articulated गाडी कि consists of a towing engine, known as a tractor in the United राज्य और truck in many अन्य places, संलग्न to एक or more semi-trailers to carry भाड़ा.
it is भी ज्ञात as a transport in कनाडा, प्रधान प्रस्तावक in Australia, सेमी, tractor-trailer, truck and ट्रेलर, transfer truck, 18-wheeler, mack ट्रक, बिग रिग in the United राज्य, or artic, short लिये articulated लारी, in ब्रिटेन and आयरलैंड.
A semi-trailer does नहीं trail completely behind the towing गाडी, but is संलग्न at a point कि is just आगे of the rear-most धुरी of the towing ईकाई.
इस is done so that a fraction of the वज़न of the ट्रेलर is carried by the प्रधान mover.
इस arrangement अर्थात् कि both tractor and semi-trailer होगा have a distinctly different डिज़ाइन than a rigid ट्रक and ट्रेलर.

तीन different kinds of गेहूं और rye आटा
आटा is a powder which is बना by grinding खाद्यान्न दाने, or other बीज or roots ( जैसे कसावा ).
It is the main ingredient of ब्रैड, जिससे is a staple food लिये अनेक संस्कृतियों, बनाना the उपलब्धता of पर्याप्त supplies of flour a major economic और political समस्या at विभिन्न टाइम्स throughout इतिहास.
गेहूं flour is एक of the most important foods in यूरोपीय, उत्तर अमरीकी, मध्य पूर्वी, Indian and North African संस्कृतियों, और is the धमक संघटक in सबसे of their styles of breads और pastries.
जबकि wheat is the सबसे आम आधार लिये flour, corn flour रै महरूम important in Mesoamerican cuisine since प्राचीन टाइम्स, और remains a स्टेपल throughout the americas.
Rye आटा is an important constituent of bread in much of सेंट्रल यूरोपीय, और rice can also be used in आटा, हालांकि इस is relatively uncommon.
दिल rate is the क्रमांक of heartbeats प्रति unit of समय, typically expressed as beats प्रति minute ( bpm ).
Heart rate can vary as the देह 's need to absorb oxygen और excrete कार्बन डाइऑक्साइड changes, ऐसे as दौरान physical exercise, sleep, बीमारी, or as a result of ingesting दवाएँ :
सेंट्रल बेचैन प्रणाली stimulants ऐसे as amphetamines increase heart रेट.
Central nervous प्रणाली depressants or sedatives decreases the दिल rate ( अलावा इससे कुछ विशेषकर strange ones साथ equally अजीब प्रभाव, ऐसे as केटामाइन which can कारण - amongst अनेक other things - stimulant-like प्रभाव such as tachycardia ).
There are अनेक तरीके in which the दिल rate speeds up or slows down.
सबसे involve stimulant-like endorphins और hormones होने released in the दिमाग, अनेक of जिससे are those that हैं 'forced'/'enticed ' आउट by the ingestion and प्रसंस्करण of दवाएँ.
due to individuals having a constant रक्त volume, एक of the physiological तरीके to उद्धार अधिक oxygen to an organ is to increase दिल rate to परमिट रक्त to pass by the organ more often.
सामान्य resting दिल दरों range इससे 60-100 bpm.
Bradycardia is defined as a resting heart रेट नीचे 60 bpm.
However, दिल दरों इससे 50 to 60 bpm हैं आम among स्वस्थ people और do not necessarily आवश्यकता खास attention.
Tachycardia is पारिभाषित as a resting heart रेट ऊपर 100 bpm, हालांकि persistent बाकी दरों between 80-100 bpm, mainly if they are present during sleep, may be signs of हाइपरथाइरॉयडिज़्म or anemia ( देखिए below ).

a carriage is a wheeled गाडी लिये लोगों, प्रायः horse-drawn ; litters ( palanquins ) और सेडान कुर्सियां are excluded, चूंकि they are wheelless वाहनों.
the carriage is especially designed for निजी passenger use and लिये comfort or elegance, हालांकि कुछ हैं also प्रयुक्त to हस्तांतरण goods.
It may be light, smart and fast or भारी, विशाल और आरामदायक.
carriages सामान्यतः have suspension using पत्ता स्रोतों, अंडाकार स्रोतों ( in the 19th सदी ) or चमड़े strapping.
A public यात्री गाडी होता नहीं प्रायः be पुकारा a carriage – शर्तें for such include stagecoach, charabanc and omnibus.
working vehicles ऐसे as the ( four-wheeled ) वैगन and ( two-wheeled ) कार्ट share महत्वपूर्ण भाग of the इतिहास of the carriage, as is the तेज़ ( two-wheeled ) रथ.
The 2004 Indian समंदर earthquake was an undersea megathrust भूकंप कि occurred at 00:58:53 UTC on Sunday, 26 December 2004, साथ an epicentre बंद the वेस्ट coast of सुमात्रा, इंडोनेशिया.
the quake itself is ज्ञात by the वैज्ञानिक community as the sumatra–andaman भूकंप.
The resulting सुनामी थी दिए विभिन्न names, सहित the 2004 Indian समंदर सुनामी, दक्षिण एशियाई सुनामी, इंडोनेशियाई tsunami, और the Boxing दिन tsunami.
The भूकंप थी caused by subduction और triggered a श्रेणी of devastating tsunamis साथ the coasts of सबसे landmasses bordering the भारतीय Ocean, हत्या over 230,000 people in चौदह देशों, and inundating coastal समुदायों with लहरें up to ऊँची.
it was एक of the deadliest प्राकृतिक आपदाओं in अंकित history.
इंडोनेशिया थी the hardest-hit देश, followed by श्री Lanka, इण्डिया, and Thailand.
साथ a परिमाण of mw 9.1–9.3, it is the third largest earthquake कभी अंकित on a seismograph.
the भूकंप था the longest अवधि of faulting ever observed, between 8.3 और 10 मिनट्स.
it caused the संपूर्ण planet to vibrate as much as और triggered other earthquakes as far away as अलास्का.
Its epicentre थी between Simeulue और mainland इंडोनेशिया.
the plight of the प्रभावित लोगों and देशों prompted a worldwide humanitarian जवाब.
in all, the विश्वव्यापी community दान more than $ 14 billion ( 2004 US $ ) in humanitarian aid.
Steam rising इससे the nesjavellir Geothermal शक्ति स्टेशन in आइसलैंड.
geothermal energy is थर्मल उर्जा generated और भंडारित in the Earth.
Thermal उर्जा is the उर्जा कि determines the temperature of matter.
The geothermal energy of the धरती 's क्रस्ट originates from the असली formation of the planet ( 20 % ) और from रेडियोसक्रिय क्षय of खनिज ( 80 % ).
the geothermal gradient, जिससे is the अंतर in तापमान between the कोर of the ग्रह और इसके सतह, ड्राइव a निरन्तर conduction of thermal energy in the रूप of ऊष्मा from the कोर to the सतह.
the adjective geothermal originates इससे the Greek roots γη ( ge ), अर्थ धरती, and θερμος ( thermos ), meaning hot.
at the core of the धरती, थर्मल energy is निर्मित by रेडियोसक्रिय decay और temperatures may पहुँचें over 5000 °c ( 9,000 °f ).
ऊष्मा conducts इससे the कोर to surrounding cooler चट्टान.
the ऊँची तापमान और दबाव कारण कुछ rock to melt, creating magma संवहन upward चूंकि it is हल्का than the solid चट्टान.
the मैग्मा heats rock और जल in the क्रस्ट, sometimes up to 370 °C ( 700 °f ).
From hot springs, geothermal energy रै been प्रयुक्त लिये स्नान since Paleolithic times और लिये space हीटिंग since प्राचीन रोमन टाइम्स, लकिन it is अभी बेहतर known लिये electricity पीढी.
Worldwide, about 10,715 megawatts ( MW ) of geothermal शक्ति is ऑनलाइन in 24 देशों.
an additional 28 gigawatts of सीधा geothermal heating क्षमता is संस्थापित for ज़िला हीटिंग, space heating, spas, industrial प्रक्रियाओं, desalination और agricultural applications.
Geothermal power is cost प्रभावी, विश्वसनीय, चिरस्थायी, and environmentally दोस्ताना, लकिन has historically been सीमित to areas निकट tectonic थाली boundaries.
हाल technological अग्रिम have dramatically विस्तारित the range and आकार of viable संसाधन, विशेषकर लिये applications ऐसे as घर हीटिंग, खोलने a potential लिये widespread exploitation.
Geothermal wells release greenhouse गैसों फंस deep within the earth, लकिन ये emissions are much निम्नतर प्रति energy unit than those of fossil fuels.
as a परिणाम, geothermal power has the संभावित to सहायता mitigate वैश्विक warming if widely तैनात in प्लेस of fossil fuels.
the Earth 's geothermal संसाधन हैं theoretically अधिक than adequate to supply मानवता 's उर्जा needs, लकिन only a बहुत small भिन्न may be profitably शोषित.
खुदाई and खोजी for गहन resources is बहुत महंगी.
forecasts for the future of geothermal power निर्भर on assumptions about प्रौद्योगिकी, उर्जा prices, subsidies, and ब्याज rates.
Pilot programs like EWEB 's ग्राहक ऑप्ट in ग्रीन Power कार्यक्रम show कि ग्राहक होता be willing to अदा a little more for a renewable उर्जा source जैसे geothermal.
लकिन as a परिणाम of सरकारी assisted शोध और उद्योग experience, the cost of generating geothermal power रै decreased by 25 % over the पास्ट two decades.
in 2001, geothermal energy लागत between two and टेन cents प्रति kwh.
the पद घन foot is an इम्पीरियल and us प्रथागत ( non- मीट्रिक ) unit of आवाज़, प्रयुक्त in the United राज्य और the United किंगडम.
It is पारिभाषित as the आवाज़ of a घन with sides of एक foot ( 0.3048 m ) in लंबाई.

Hồ chí मिन्ह ( उत्तरी वियतनामी उच्चारण :, दक्षिणी वियतनामी उच्चारण : ) ; 19 May 1890 – 2 September 1969 ), born Nguyễn Sinh Cung और भी known as nguyễn tất Thành and nguyễn Ái quốc, थी a वियतनामी communist revolutionary leader who was प्रधान मंत्री ( 1945–1955 ) और president ( 1945–1969 ) of the लोकतांत्रिक Republic of वियतनाम ( उत्तर वियतनाम ).
he थी a कुंजी figure in the foundation of the लोकतांत्रिक गणतंत्र of वियतनाम in 1945, as खूब as the people’s Army of वियतनाम ( pavn ) और the Việt Cộng ( NLF or VC ) during the वियतनाम War.
he led the việt Minh independence movement इससे 1941 onward, establishing the कम्युनिस्ट -ruled Democratic गणतंत्र of Vietnam in 1945 and defeating the फ्रेंच Union in 1954 at the बैटल of điện Biên phủ.
he officially stepped bas इससे power in 1955 due to स्वास्थ्य समस्याएं, लकिन remained a अत्यधिक दृश्य figurehead और प्रेरणा for those वियतनामी लड़ लिये उसके cause—a संयुक्त, कम्युनिस्ट Vietnam—until उसके मौत.
बाद the युद्ध, Saigon, पूंजी of the Republic of Vietnam, थी renamed hồ chí Minh नगर.

बिक्री taxes in the United राज्य हैं कर placed on the sale or lease of goods and services in the संयुक्त राज्य.
जबकि no नेशनल सामान्य sales tax exists, the संघीय सरकारी levies अनेक नेशनल चयनात्मक sales taxes on the sale or पट्टे of particular goods and services.
furthermore, forty-five states, the ज़िला of Columbia, and Guam थोपने सामान्य बिक्री taxes that लागू to the sale or पट्टे of सबसे goods और कुछ सेवाएं, and states भी may levy चयनात्मक sales taxes on the बिक्री or lease of particular goods or services.
राज्य may also delegate to local governments the authority to थोपने additional सामान्य or selective sales taxes.
बिक्री कर is गणना by multiplying the purchase दाम by the लागू कर rate.
कर दरों vary widely by क्षेत्राधिकार and दायरा from less than 1 % to over 10 %.
बिक्री tax is एकत्रित by the विक्रेता at the समय of sale.
उपयोग कर is स्वः assessed by a खरीदार जो has नहीं paid बिक्री tax on a taxable खरीदें.
Unlike the value added कर, a बिक्री tax is imposed तभी एकबार, at the retail स्तर.
However, in मामले where items are बेची at खुदरा more than एकबार, such as प्रयुक्त cars, the sales tax can be charged on the same मद indefinitely.
The परिभाषा of खुदरा sales और कया goods और सेवाएं हैं taxable vary among the राज्य.
nearly सब jurisdictions provide numerous श्रेणी of goods और services that हैं exempt from बिक्री tax, or taxed at reduced rates.
the खरीदें of goods लिये further manufacture or लिये पुनर्विक्रय is uniformly exempt from sales कर.
सबसे jurisdictions exempt food sold in किराना स्टोर्स, नुस्खा medications, और अनेक agricultural आपूर्तियाँ.
Sales कर, including those imposed by लोकल governments, हैं generally administered at the राज्य level.
राज्य imposing बिक्री कर आवश्यकता खुदरा विक्रेता to collect कर इससे ग्राहक, file returns, and remit the tax to the state.
प्रक्रियात्मक rules vary widely.
Sellers generally must collect कर इससे in-state purchasers जबतक the क्रेता provides an exemption प्रमाणपत्र.
सबसे states allow or require इलेक्ट्रॉनिक remittance.
a central processing ईकाई ( CPU ), also referred to as a सेंट्रल processor ईकाई, is the hardware within a कंप्यूटर that carries आउट the instructions of a computer कार्यक्रम by performing the basic अंकगणितीय, लॉजिकल, and input/output परिचालन of the system.
The पद रै महरूम in use in the computer industry at least since the early 1960s.
The रूप, design, और क्रियान्वयन of cpu have बदला over the कोर्स of उनके इतिहास, but उनके आधारभूत operation remains much the वही.
a कंप्यूटर can have अधिक than एक cpu ; इस is called multiprocessing.
Some एकीकृत circuits ( ICs ) can contain अनेक CPUs on a single चिप ; those ics are पुकारा multi-core processors.
Two ठेठ components of a cpu हैं the arithmetic लॉजिक ईकाई ( alu ), which performs गणित और logical परिचालन, और the कंट्रोल ईकाई ( cu ), जिससे extracts निर्देश from memory और decodes and चलाता them, calling on the alu जब necessary.
नहीं all computational प्रणालियों rely on a सेंट्रल प्रसंस्करण unit.
an सरणी processor or vector प्रोसेसर has अनेक समानांतर कम्प्यूटिंग तत्व, with no एक ईकाई माना the `` center ''.
in the distributed computing मॉडल, problems are हल by a वितरित interconnected set of processors.
RFID chip next to a अनाज of राइस.
This चिप contains a radio-frequency electromagnetic field कुंडली that modulates an बाह्य magnetic फ़ील्ड to transfer a coded पहचान क्रमांक जब queried by a reader यंत्र.
This small type is incorporated in उपभोक्ता products, and implanted in pets, लिये identification purposes.
Radio-frequency पहचान ( rfid ) is the wireless non-contact use of radio-frequency इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक फ़ील्ड to ट्रांसफ़र आंकड़ा, for the purposes of automatically identifying and tracking tags संलग्न to objects.
The टैग contain electronically भंडारित information.
कुछ टैग हैं संचालित और पढ़ा at short सीमाएँ ( a few meters ) via चुम्बकीय फ़ील्ड ( इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक प्रेरण ).
अन्य उपयोग a लोकल power source ऐसे as a बैटरी, or else have no battery लकिन collect उर्जा from the interrogating EM field, और तब अधिनियम as a passive transponder to emit microwaves or UHF रेडियो लहरें ( i.e., इलेक्ट्रोमैग्नेटिक radiation at ऊँची frequencies ).
बैटरी संचालित टैग may operate at hundreds of meters.
नापसंद a बार कोड, the tag करता not necessarily need to be within लकीर of sight of the reader, और may be embedded in the tracked object.
rfid tags are प्रयुक्त in many उद्योग.
An RFID टैग attached to an ऑटोमोबाइल during production can be प्रयुक्त to track its प्रगति through the सभा line.
दवाएँ can be tracked through warehouses.
पशुधन and पालतु may have टैग injected, allowing धनात्मक identification of the animal.
चूंकि rfid tags can be attached to कपडे, possessions, or भी implanted within लोगों, the possibility of reading personally-linked information without सहमति रै raised privacy चिंताएं.
Overtime is the amount of समय किसी works परे सामान्य working घंटों.
सामान्य hours may be संकल्पित in अनेक रास्ताs:
by कस्टम ( कया is माना स्वस्थ or reasonable by समाज ),
by practices of a दिए व्यापार or profession,
by legislation,
by अनुबंध between नियोक्ता और workers or their representatives.
सबसे राष्ट्र have overtime labor laws designed to dissuade or prevent नियोक्ता इससे forcing उनके employees to work excessively long hours.
These कानून may लो into खाता other considerations than the humanitarian, such as preserving the स्वास्थ्य of workers so that वे may continue to be productive, or increasing the overall level of employment in the अर्थव्यवस्था.
One common approach to regulating overtime is to require employers to pay workers at a उच्चतर hourly रेट लिये ओवरटाइम कार्य.
Companies may choose to pay workers उच्चतर overtime अदा भी if नहीं obliged to do so by विधि, विशेषकर if वे मानना कि they फेस a पिछड़ा झुकने सप्लाई curve of श्रमिक.
Overtime pay दरों can cause मजदूर to कार्य longer hours than वे would at a चपटा hourly रेट.
ओवरटाइम laws, attitudes toward ओवरटाइम and घंटों of work vary greatly इससे देश to देश and between अलग आर्थिक सेक्टर.

force-directed graph drawing algorithms are a class of algorithms लिये drawing graphs in an aesthetically pleasing way.
उनके purpose is to स्थिति the नोड of a आलेख in two-dimensional or three-dimensional स्पेस so that all the किनारे हैं of अधिक or less बराबर length और there are as few crossing किनारे as possible, by assigning forces among the नियत of किनारे और the set of नोड, आधारित on their relative स्थितियाँ, और तब using these forces either to simulate the motion of the edges और nodes or to minimize उनके energy.
जबकि आलेख drawing can be a मुश्किल problem, force-directed algorithms, होने शारीरिक simulations, प्रायः require no खास knowledge about आलेख theory ऐसे as planarity.
खरीदना शक्ति ( sometimes retroactively पुकारा adjusted for महंगाई ) is the amount of goods or सेवाएं that can be खरीदा साथ a unit of करेंसी.
For उदाहरण, if तुम had taken one डालर to a स्टोर in the 1950s, you होता have महरूम समर्थ to buy a वृहद number of वस्तुएं than तुम होता आज, indicating that तुम would have था a greater खरीदना शक्ति in the 1950s.
Currency can be either a commodity धन, like सुनहरा or चांदी, or fiat currency, or free-floating market-valued करेंसी like us डॉलर.
as आदम Smith विख्यात, having धन देता एक the क्षमता to `` command '' अन्य ' labor, so खरीदना शक्ति to कुछ extent is power over अन्य लोगों, to the extent that वे are willing to व्यापार their मजदूर or goods लिये money or currency.

महंगाई does नहीं always imply गिरना purchasing power of one 's money आय चूंकि it may वृद्धि faster than the price level.
A उच्चतर रियल income अर्थात् a उच्चतर purchasing शक्ति since real income refers to the income समायोजित लिये महंगाई.
लिये a दाम index, इसके value in the base साल is usually normalized to a मान of 100.

so, by परिभाषा the purchasing power of a dollar decreases as the दाम स्तर rises.

a सेंट्रल प्रशासन oversees the process for the शिक्षा of children इससे kindergarten to the third और final साल of high school.
गणित, विज्ञान, कोरियाई, English, और सोशल studies are generally considered to be the most महत्वपूर्ण विषय.
सामान्यतः शारीरिक education is नहीं considered महत्वपूर्ण as it is नहीं recognised, by the generally अकादमिक elitist South Korean populace, as शिक्षा and इसलिए अनेक स्कूलों कमी high-quality gymnasiums और varsity एथलेटिक्स.
South Korea थी the first देश in the world to provide high-speed internet access to सब प्राथमिक, जूनियर, and high schools.
Although South कोरियाई विद्यार्थी प्रायः rank highly on अंतरराष्ट्रीय comparative assessments जब compared to विद्यार्थी of सबसे Western शिक्षा systems, the दक्षिण कोरियाई शिक्षा प्रणाली is criticised लिये emphasising too much upon passive learning and memorisation.
The South कोरियाई education प्रणाली is बल्कि notably सख्त and overly structured as compared to its counterparts in सबसे पश्चिमी समाजों.
Also, the व्यापकता of non-school for-profit private संस्थान such as academies or cram-schools ( hagwon [ 학원 ] ), which too emphasise on passive memorisation, as opposed to conceptual समझना, in students हैं criticised as a प्रमुख सोशल प्रॉब्लम.
the My lai Massacre (, ;,, or ) was the वियतनाम युद्ध mass हत्या of between 347 और 504 निहत्थे नागरिकों in दक्षिण Vietnam on कूच 16, 1968, by संयुक्त राज्य Army सैनिको of `` चार्ली '' कम्पनी of 1st बटालियन, 20th infantry रेजीमेंट, 11th Brigade of the Americal Division.
पीड़ितों शामिल महिलाओं, मेन, children, and infants.
कुछ of the women were gang-raped and their लाशें यहूद बाद मिला to be mutilated और many महिलाओं यहूद allegedly raped prior to the हत्याओं.
While 26 u.S. soldiers यहूद initially चार्ज साथ criminal offenses लिये उनके actions at mỹ lai, only दूसरी Lieutenant विलियम calley, a प्लाटून leader in Charlie कम्पनी, was convicted.
मिला अपराधी of हत्या 22 ग्रामीणों, he was originally given a life sentence, but तभी परोसा तीन and a half सालो अंतर्गत हाउस गिरफ़्तार.
the नरसंहार took प्लेस in the hamlets of My lai और my Khe of बेटे My village.
The event is also known as the Son My Massacre, विशेषकर in the Vietnamese राज्य मीडिया.
the u.S. सैन्य codeword लिये the `` viet cong stronghold '' थी `` Pinkville ''.
The घटना prompted वैश्विक आक्रोश जब it became पब्लिक ज्ञान in 1969.
the massacre भी increased domestic विपक्ष to the U.S. involvement in the वियतनाम युद्ध.
तीन U.S. servicemen who था आजमाया to halt the नरसंहार और protect the wounded यहूद initially denounced by several U.S. Congressmen as traitors.
They received नफ़रत mail और death खतरे and मिला mutilated पशु on their doorsteps.
The तीन यहूद later widely praised और decorated by the फौज for उनके वीर actions.

abū al-Qāsim Muḥammad इब्न ʿabd Allāh इब्न ʿAbd al-Muṭṭalib ibn Hāshim ( ) ( circa| 570 – circa| 8 जून 632 ), भी transliterated as Muhammad ( ), was a religious, राजनैतिक, और सैन्य नेता इससे मक्का who एकीकृत अरब into a single धार्मिक polity under Islam.
he is believed by Muslims और Bahá'ís to be a मेसेंजर and नबी of परमेश्वर.
मुहम्मद is almost universally माना by मुसलमान as the पिछला prophet sent by परमेश्वर लिये mankind.
non-muslims लिहाज़ मुहम्मद as the संस्थापक of Islam.
मुसलमान consider उसे to be the restorer of an unaltered असली monotheistic faith of आदम, नूह, Abraham, मूसा, Jesus, और other prophets.
Born in about 570 CE in the Arabian city of मक्का, he was अनाथ at an जल्दी आयु and brought up under the परवाह of उसके uncle Abu तालिब.
He बाद worked mostly as a व्यापारी, as well as a shepherd, और थी पहला शादीशुदा by आयु 25.
Being in the आदत of periodically retreating to a गुफा in the surrounding mountains लिये several नाइट्स of seclusion और prayer, he बाद reported कि it थी there, at age 40, that he received his first रहस्योद्घाटन इससे परमेश्वर.
तीन years बाद इस इवेंट मुहम्मद प्रारंभ उपदेश these खुलासे publicly, proclaiming that `` God is एक ``, that पूरा `` आत्मसमर्पण '' to उसे ( lit.
islām ) is the तभी way ( dīn ) स्वीकार्य to परमेश्वर, और कि he खुद थी a नबी और मेसेंजर of परमेश्वर, in the same vein as अन्य Islamic नबियों.
मुहम्मद gained few followers early on, and थी मिले साथ दुश्मनी इससे कुछ Meccan जनजातियों ; he and उसके अनुसरणकर्ता यहूद treated harshly.
to एस्केप persecution, Muhammad भेजा some of his अनुसरणकर्ता to अबीसीनिया पहले he and उसके followers in मक्का migrated to Medina ( then ज्ञात as yathrib ) in the year 622.
This इवेंट, the हिज्र, marks the beginning of the Islamic पंचांग, जिससे is also ज्ञात as the Hijri Calendar.
In मदीना, Muhammad संयुक्त the tribes अंतर्गत the संविधान of मदीना.
बाद eight years of लड़ साथ the meccan जनजातियों, his अनुसरणकर्ता, who by then था grown to 10,000, took control of मक्का in the largely शांतिपूर्ण conquest of मक्का.
He नष्ट the pagan मूर्तियों in the city और तब भेजा his अनुसरणकर्ता आउट to destroy all of the remaining pagan मंदिरों in Eastern अरब.
in 632, a few महीने बाद returning to मदीना इससे the Farewell Pilgrimage, मुहम्मद गिरी ill और died.
By the समय of उसके death, सबसे of the arabian प्रायद्वीप था converted to Islam, और he had संयुक्त अरब into a single Muslim धार्मिक polity.
the revelations ( or ayah, lit.
`` Signs [ of God ] '' ) — जिससे मुहम्मद reported receiving जबतक उसके death – form the आयतें of the कुरान, regarded by मुसलमान as the `` शब्द of God '' and around जिससे the धर्म is based.
besides the कुरान, मुहम्मद 's जीवन ( सिरा ) और परंपराओं ( सुन्नत ) are भी upheld by Muslims as the स्त्रोत of शरीयत विधि.
They discuss मुहम्मद और other नबियों of islam साथ reverence, adding the phrase सलाम be upon him whenever their names हैं उल्लेखित.
जबकि conceptions of मुहम्मद in medieval Christendom और premodern टाइम्स यहूद largely ऋणात्मक, appraisals in आधुनिक इतिहास have महरूम far less so.
इस is a सूची of tables of the सत्यापित oldest लोगों in the world in ordinal rank, ऐसे as oldest व्यक्ति or oldest man.
in these tables, a supercentenarian is considered 'verified ' if his or her claim रै been validated by an international देह कि specifically सौदे in आयु शोध, ऐसे as the Gerontology शोध Group ( GRG ) or गिनीज संसार Records.
The longest unambiguously documented इंसान lifespan is कि of Jeanne calment of फ़्रांस ( 1875–1997 ), जो died at आयु 122 सालो, 164 दिनों.
She मिले विंसेंट वैन gogh when she थी 12 or 13.
इस led to news मीडिया ध्यान in 1985, after calment turned 110.
subsequent छानबीन मिला दस्तावेज़ीकरण for Calment 's आयु, beyond कोई उचित question, in the रिकॉर्ड of her native नगर, Arles, France.
अधिक evidence of Calment 's जीवनकाल has महरूम उत्पादित than लिये any अन्य supercentenarian ; उसके case serves as an archetype in the methodology लिये verifying the आयु of the संसार 's oldest लोगों.
The longest undisputed जीवनकाल for पुरूष supercentenarians is कि of jiroemon किमुरा, who फिलहाल जीवनदान in जापानी and is आयु as of.
चूंकि the मौत of 115-year बूढ़ा Dina manfredini of the संयुक्त States, on 17 दिसम्बर 2012, Kimura, born 19 April 1897, is the oldest जीना person in the world जिनकी आयु can be documented.
he रै also महरूम the oldest living man since the मौत of 114-year बूढ़ा Walter Breuning on 14 अप्रैल 2011.
चूंकि the death of 115-year बूढ़ा Koto okubo of जापानी on 12 January 2013, the oldest living स्त्री रै महरूम -year-old misao okawa, भी from जापानी, born on 5 March 1898.

the Civil Rights गति was a freedom संघर्ष by अफ़्रीकी Americans in the 1950s और 1960s to लाभ समता.
