भारी मेटल ( प्रायः referred to as metal ) is a genre of rock music कि विकसित in the लेट 1960s and जल्दी 1970s, largely in the संयुक्त Kingdom and in the United राज्य.
साथ जड़ें in ब्लूज़ चट्टान और psychedelic चट्टान, the bands कि created भारी metal developed a thick, विशाल sound, characterized by अत्यधिक amplified distortion, विस्तारित गिटार solos, emphatic बीट्स, और overall loudness.
भारी मेटल गीत और प्रदर्शन styles are generally संबद्ध with masculinity और machismo.
The पहला भारी metal bands such as led zeppelin, गहन Purple और Black Sabbath attracted विशाल ऑडियंस, हालांकि they were प्रायः derided by critics, a औकात common throughout the इतिहास of the विधा.
in the mid-1970s यहूदा पुजारी helped spur the genre 's एवोल्यूशन by discarding much of इसके ब्लूज़ influence ; motörhead introduced a punk rock sensibility और an increasing emphasis on गति.
Bands in the नई वेव of British भारी Metal such as Iron Maiden followed in a similar vein.
पहले the समाप्त of the decade, भारी metal fans became ज्ञात as `` metalheads `` or `` headbangers ``.
दौरान the 1980s, glam metal became a commercial फ़ोर्स साथ groups जैसे Mötley crüe and ज़हर.
Underground दृश्यों produced an array of अधिक चरम, आक्रामक शैलियाँ : thrash मेटल broke into the मुख्यधारा साथ bands ऐसे as मेटालिका, मेगाडेथ, slayer, और Anthrax, while other शैलियाँ of the सबसे extreme subgenres of मेटल जैसे मौत मेटल और black metal remain subcultural phenomena.
चूंकि the mid-1990s, लोकप्रिय styles ऐसे as nu metal, which often incorporates तत्व of grunge and हिप हॉप ; and metalcore, which मिश्रणों extreme metal साथ हार्डकोर पंक, have further expanded the परिभाषा of the विधा.
the far-right ( भी known as the चरम सही ) refers to the highest उपाधि of rightism in right-wing politics.
दूर right राजनीती involves support of दमदार or complete सोशल hierarchy in समाज, और supports supremacy of certain individuals or समूह deemed to be innately superior or अस्तबलों जो हैं to be अधिक valued than those deemed to be innately inferior or अवांछनीय.
The दूर सही 's वकालत of supremacism is आधारित on कया its adherents perceive as स्वाभाविक विशेषताएँ of people कि can नहीं be changed.
इस stands as a पाइंट of difference साथ the centre-right 's attribution of behaviours, ऐसे as आलस्य or decadence, as the primary स्त्रोत of social inequalities.
the centre right—unlike the दूर right—claims that लोगों can समाप्त their behavioural हीनता through बदलना उनके आदतें and choices.
The असली far सही, which उभरा in फ़्रांस after the फ्रेंच क्रान्ति, refused to accept the French गणतंत्र और supported a counter-revolution to restore the फ्रेंच monarchy and aristocracy.
The दूर right is commonly संबद्ध साथ persons or समूह जो थाम चरम राष्ट्रवादी, xenophobic, जातिवाद, religious fundamentalist or प्रतिक्रियावादी दृश्य.
the सबसे extreme-right movements have pursued दमन and नरसंहार against समूह of लोगों on the आधार of their alleged हीनता.
Thomas hobbes of malmesbury ( 5 अप्रैल 1588 – 4 December 1679 ), in कुछ older ग्रन्थ थामस Hobbs of malmsbury, थी an अंग्रेज़ी philosopher, बेहतरीन ज्ञात आज for उसके कार्य on राजनैतिक philosophy.
His 1651 book Leviathan स्थापित the न्यास लिये most of पश्चिमी राजनैतिक दर्शनशास्त्र इससे the परिप्रेक्ष्य of सोशल contract सिद्धान्त.
hobbes थी a चैंपियन of absolutism लिये the sovereign, लकिन he also developed कुछ of the fundamentals of यूरोपीय liberal विचार : the सही of the individual ; the प्राकृतिक समता of all मेन ; the artificial अक्षर of the राजनैतिक अनुक्रम ( which led to the बाद distinction between civil society और the राज्य ) ; the दृश्य कि सब legitimate राजनैतिक power जरूर be `` representative '' and based on the consent of the लोगों ; and a उदार निर्वचन of law जिससे leaves people फ़्री to do whatever the law does नहीं explicitly forbid.
he थी एक of the founders of आधुनिक political दर्शनशास्त्र.
His समझना of इंसानो as being पदार्थ and गति, obeying the वही physical कानून as other matter और motion, remains influential ; और उसके account of इंसान nature as self-interested सहयोग, और of political समुदायों as होने आधारित upon a `` social अनुबंध `` remains one of the प्रमुख विषय of राजनैतिक दर्शनशास्त्र.
in addition to राजनैतिक philosophy, hobbes भी contributed to a विविध सरणी of अन्य fields, सहित history, भूगोल, the भौतिकी of gases, धर्मशास्त्र, आचार, and general philosophy.
Emotional प्रज्ञा ( EI ) is the क्षमता to पहचानो, assess, and control the भाव of oneself, of अन्य, and of समूह.
it can be विभाजित into क्षमता ei और trait EI.
क्षमता ei is प्रायः measured using अधिकतम प्रदर्शन tests and has stronger संबंध साथ traditional प्रज्ञा, whereas trait ei is usually measured using self-report questionnaires और has stronger relationships साथ personality.
आलोचनाओं have centered on whether ei is a real प्रज्ञा और whether it रै वृद्धिशील वैध over IQ और the बिग पाँच व्यक्तित्व traits.
आनुवंशिकता is the गुजर of traits to offspring from इसके अभिभावक or पूर्वज.
इस is the प्रक्रम by which an औलाद कोशिका or सजीव acquires or becomes predisposed to the विशेषताएँ of इसके जनक cell or सजीव.
through heredity, विसंगतियाँ exhibited by individuals can accumulate and कारण कुछ प्रजाति to evolve.
the पढ़ाई of आनुवंशिकता in biology is called आनुवंशिकी, जिससे शामिल the field of epigenetics.
For United राज्य individual income tax, समायोजित सकल income ( agi ) is total gross income ऋण विशिष्ट reductions.
taxable आय is समायोजित gross आय ऋण भत्तों for personal छूटों and itemized deductions.
लिये सबसे individual tax उद्देश्य, AGI is more relevant than gross income.
सकल आय is sales दाम of goods or प्रॉपर्टी, minus cost of the property sold, प्लस अन्य income.
it शामिल मजदूरी, ब्याज, dividends, कारोबार income, rental income, and सब अन्य प्रकार of income.
समायोजित gross आय is gross आय कम deductions इससे a business or rental activity और 21 other विशिष्ट वस्तुएं.
अनेक deductions ( e.g. medical expenses और विविध itemized deductions ) हैं limited based on a प्रतिशत of agi.
निश्चित phase outs, including those of निम्नतर कर rates and itemized deductions, are based on स्तर of AGI.
अनेक states आधार राज्य आय tax on agi साथ निश्चित deductions.

A टेलीफोन उपसर्ग is the पहला नियत of अंक of a टेलीफोन क्रमांक ; in the उत्तर American क्रमांकन योजना countries ( देश कोड 1 ), it is the first तीन अंक of a seven-digit फोन number.
in अन्य देशों दोनो the उपसर्ग और the number may have अलग lengths.
It shows जिससे exchange the बाकी संख्याएँ refer to.
a पूरा टेलीफोन क्रमांक is usually बना up of country code ( required लिये अंतरराष्ट्रीय calls only ), area कोड ( required लिये काल्स between टेलीफोन areas ), prefix, और सदस्य क्रमांक.
कुछ places restrict certain prefixes to fax संख्याएँ or cell फोन only ; in other places ऐसे समर्पित prefixes are नहीं प्रयुक्त.
as टेलीफोन technology advanced, the precise significance of the prefix became blurred in many स्थान ; 485 in London, uk, was एकबार the GULliver exchange, but now 44207485xxxx is बस considered एक of अनेक क्रमांक ब्लॉक served by the clken Kentish Town exchange ; 4420770703xx is another.
metformin ( bp, pronounced, ; originally sold as glucophage ) is an oral antidiabetic ड्रग in the biguanide क्लास.
It is the first-line ड्रग of चुनाव लिये the treatment of प्रकार 2 diabetes, in particular, in overweight and मोटे लोगों and those with normal गुर्दा फलन.
इसके use in गर्भकालीन मधुमेह has महरूम सीमित by safety concerns.
it is also प्रयुक्त in the उपचार of polycystic ovary सिंड्रोम, और रै been investigated लिये other रोगों where इंसुलिन resistance may be an important फ़ैक्टर.
metformin works by suppressing ग्लूकोज production by the liver.
metformin is the तभी antidiabetic drug कि रै महरूम conclusively दिखाया to prevent the cardiovascular जटिलताओं of मधुमेह.
it helps reduce ldl cholesterol and triglyceride levels, और is नहीं associated with वज़न gain.
, metformin is one of तभी दो मौखिक antidiabetics in the World स्वास्थ्य Organization Model List of Essential दवाइयाँ ( the अन्य होने glibenclamide ).
जब prescribed appropriately, metformin कल्याणकारी few adverse प्रभाव ( the most common is जठरांत्र परेशान ) और is associated with a low risk of hypoglycemia.
लैक्टिक acidosis ( a buildup of lactate in the blood ) can be a गंभीर concern in overdose and जब it is विहित to लोगों साथ contraindications, लकिन otherwise, there is no significant रिस्क.
पहला synthesized और मिला to reduce blood sugar in the 1920s, metformin was forgotten for the अगला दो दशकों as research shifted to insulin और अन्य antidiabetic दवाएँ.
ब्याज in metformin was rekindled in the late 1940s after अनेक reports that it could reduce रक्त sugar levels in people, and in 1957, फ्रेंच physician Jean Sterne प्रकाशित the पहला नैदानिक विचारण of metformin as a उपचार for मधुमेह.
It थी introduced to the संयुक्त किंगडम in 1958, Canada in 1972, और the United राज्य in 1995.
metformin is अभी believed to be the most widely prescribed antidiabetic ड्रग in the संसार ; in the संयुक्त राज्य अलोन, अधिक than 48 लाख prescriptions यहूद भर in 2010 लिये इसके generic formulations.
the माउंट rushmore नेशनल मेमोरियल is a मूर्तिकला carved into the ग्रेनाइट फेस of माउंट rushmore near Keystone, दक्षिण Dakota, in the संयुक्त States.
Sculpted by danish-american Gutzon borglum और उसके बेटे, lincoln borglum, माउंट Rushmore सुविधाएँ sculptures of the heads of four संयुक्त राज्य presidents : जार्ज वॉशिंगटन, Thomas Jefferson, Theodore रूज़वेल्ट और अब्राहम lincoln.
the संपूर्ण memorial कवर and is ऊपर समुद्र level.
the tallest पहाड़ in the region is harney शिखर ( ).
दक्षिण डकोटा historian दोने Robinson is credited साथ conceiving the idea of नक्काशी the likenesses of famous लोगों into the Black पहाड़ियाँ region of South Dakota in अनुक्रम to promote पर्यटन in the प्रदेश.
Robinson 's आरंभिक idea was to sculpt the Needles ; however, gutzon Borglum अस्वीकृत the needles site because of the ग़रीब quality of the ग्रेनाइट और दमदार विपक्ष इससे environmentalists और Native अमरीकी समूह.
वे settled on the माउंट Rushmore location, which also रै the लाभ of facing southeast लिये maximum sun एक्सपोज़र.
रॉबिन्सन wanted it to विशेषता western नायक जैसे लुईस और Clark, रेड बादल and भैंस विधेयक कोड़ी लकिन borglum decided the sculpture चाहिए have a अधिक national फ़ोकस, और chose the चार presidents जिनकी likenesses होता be carved into the पहाड़.
After securing federal funding, निर्माण on the memorial began in 1927, और the presidents ' चेहरों यहूद समाप्त between 1934 और 1939.
upon gutzon borglum 's death in March 1941, उसके बेटे Lincoln borglum took over निर्माण.
हालांकि the आरंभिक अवधारणा called for each president to be चित्रित इससे head to कमर, कमी of funding मजबूर construction to समाप्त in late अक्तूबर 1941.
the u.S. नेशनल Park सेवा took control of the memorial in 1933, जबकि it थी स्टिल अंतर्गत निर्माण, और रै प्रबंधित the memorial to the present दिन.
it attracts nearly तीन लाख लोगों annually.

a shirt, dress कमीज़, button-front, button-front shirt, or button-up shirt is a garment साथ a कॉलर, a full-length खोलने at the front from the कॉलर to the हेम, और टाँक साथ cuffs.
शर्ट हैं predominantly प्रयुक्त by men, since women प्रायः पहनें blouses.
the सामने खोलने is fastened using buttons or studs, और the cuffs close साथ buttons or कफ कड़ी.
शर्ट हैं सामान्यतः बना from woven cloth, and हैं प्रायः accompanied by a jacket और टाई, लिये example with a सूट or formalwear, लकिन shirts हैं also worn more casually.
in अंग्रेजों English, पोशाक कमीज़ means specifically the more औपचारिक evening परिधान worn साथ black- or white- टाई, भी discussed नीचे.
कुछ of these औपचारिक शर्ट have stiff fronts and detachable collars attached साथ कॉलर studs.
The पद `` button-down '' ( which refers a प्रकार of कमीज़ जिससे रै a collar fastened bas by buttons ) is sometimes प्रयुक्त in error to लागू to all शर्ट ( साथ or बगैर buttoned bas छल्लों ), being प्रयुक्त as a synonym for `` button-up '' or `` button-front ''.

निकोलस poussin ( ; 15 June 1594 – 19 November 1665 ) थी the अग्रणी चित्रकार of the शास्त्रीय फ्रेंच बरॉक style, हालांकि he खर्च most of his working life in रोम.
उसके work is characterized by स्पष्टता, logic, and order, and favors लकीर over color.
जबतक the 20th century he remained a प्रमुख प्रेरणा for such classically उन्मुख कलाकारों as Jacques-Louis दाउद, jean-auguste-dominique Ingres और पॉल cézanne.
he worked in रोम लिये a circle of अग्रणी collectors there और elsewhere, except लिये a छोटी period when कार्डिनल रिचलू ordered him back to France to serve as पहला Painter to the King.
Most of उसके works हैं इतिहास paintings of धार्मिक or पौराणिक विषय कि बहुत प्रायः have a विशाल landscape तत्व.

A statute is a औपचारिक written enactment of a विधान authority कि governs a state, नगर, or county.
typically, statutes कमांड or prohibit something, or घोषित नीति.
The शब्द is often प्रयुक्त to फर्क विधि बना by legislative लाशें इससे मामला विधि, decided by न्यायालयों, और regulations जारी by सरकारी एजेंसियों.
statutes हैं sometimes referred to as विधान or `` ब्लैक अक्षर law. ''
as a सोर्स of विधि, statutes हैं माना primary प्राधिकार ( as opposed to द्वितीयक प्राधिकार ).
ideally सब statutes जरूर be in harmony साथ the आधारभूत law of the जमीन ( संवैधानिक ).
This शब्द is प्रयुक्त in contradistinction to the आम विधि.
statutes acquire उनके फ़ोर्स इससे the समय of their passage, however जबतक otherwise provided.
Statutes हैं of अनेक kinds ; namely, पब्लिक or निजी.
Declaratory or remedial.
अस्थाई or perpetual.
A अस्थाई statute is one which is सीमित in its duration at the समय of its enactment.
It continues in फ़ोर्स जबतक the time of इसके limitation has समाप्त, जबतक sooner repealed.
A perpetual statute is one लिये the फिराकर of जिससे वहीँ is no limited समय, हालांकि it may नहीं be expressly घोषित to be so.
if, however, a statute जिससे किया नहीं itself contain कोई limitation is to be governed by another जिससे is अस्थाई तभी, the पूर्व होगा भी be अस्थाई और dependent upon the existence of the latter.
पहले a statute becomes विधि in some देशों, it must be agreed upon by the highest कार्यपालिका in the सरकारी, and आखिरकार published as भाग of a code.
in many देशों, statutes हैं organized in topical इंतजाम ( or `` संहिताबद्ध '' ) भीतर publications पुकारा कोड, ऐसे as the संयुक्त States Code.
In many राष्ट्र statutory विधि is विशिष्ट इससे and अधीनस्थ to संवैधानिक law.
the external iliac धमनियों are दो major arteries जिससे bifurcate बंद the common iliac धमनियों अग्रवर्ती to the sacroiliac संयुक्त of the pelvis.
They proceed अग्रवर्ती और अवर साथ the medial किनारा of the psoas प्रमुख मांसपेशियां.
वे निकास the pelvic girdle posterior और inferior to the inguinal ligament about one third laterally from the प्रविष्ट पाइंट of the वंक्षण ligament on the pubic tubercle at जिससे पाइंट they हैं referred to as the नैया arteries.
The बाह्य iliac artery is प्रायः the artery used to संलग्न the renal धमनी to the प्राप्तकर्ता of a kidney प्रत्यारोपण.
Steam is a digital वितरण, digital अधिकारों management, एकाधिक and communications मंच विकसित by वाल्व Corporation.
it is used to वितरित games and सम्बन्धित मीडिया ऑनलाइन, इससे small स्वतंत्र डेवलपर to larger तन्त्र houses ; in अक्तूबर 2012, वाल्व expanded the सेवा to include non-gaming तन्त्र.
भाप provides the उपयोक्ता साथ संस्थापना और automatic प्रबन्धन of तन्त्र आरपार multiple computers, जातियाँ सुविधाएँ ऐसे as मित्रों lists और समूह, बादल saving, and in-game आवाज़ और chat कार्यक्षमता.
the software provides a freely available अनुप्रयोग programming interface, Steamworks, that डेवलपर can take लाभ of to integrate many of भाप 's functions within their software products, सहित नक़ल protection, नेटवर्किंग and matchmaking, in-game उपलब्धियाँ और micro-transactions, और support for user-created सामग्री through भाप Workshop.
हालांकि initially विकसित लिये उपयोग on microsoft खिड़कियाँ, the client रै expanded to शामिल os x और लिनक्स संस्करण, और क्लाइंट with limited कार्यक्षमता on the प्लेस्टेशन 3 console और for both आईओएस and एंड्रॉइड मोबाईल डिवाइस.
In addition to होने a सेंट्रल हब लिये गेमिंग software, Valve has created a version of भाप with altered कार्यक्षमता to be प्रयुक्त in स्कूलों for शैक्षणिक तन्त्र, सहित a परिवर्धित संस्करण of Portal 2 लिये teaching विज्ञान and नाजुक सोच lessons.
, there हैं nearly 2000 games available through भाप, and 54 लाख active user खाते.
As of जनवरी 2013, भाप रै देखी over 6.6 million संयुक्त players.
भाप रै an अनुमानित 50–70 % share of the डिजिटल distribution मार्केट लिये video खेल.

जेरी लुईस ( born March 16, 1926 ) is an अमरीकी हास्य, actor, सिंगर, film producer, screenwriter and फिल्मी निदेशक.
he is known लिये उसके slapstick ह्यूमर in film, टेलीविज़न, स्टेज and रेडियो.
he थी originally युग्म up साथ डीन मार्टिन in 1946, forming the famed कॉमेडी टोली of मार्टिन और लुईस.
in जोड to the duo 's लोकप्रिय nightclub कार्य, they स्ट्रक्चर in a कामयाब श्रेणी of comedy films for सर्वोपरि तस्वीरें.
Lewis is भी ज्ञात लिये उसके दान fund-raising telethons और स्थिति as national chairman लिये the Muscular dystrophy Association ( mda ).
लुईस रै won अनेक awards लिये lifetime उपलब्धियाँ from the अमरीकी कॉमेडी Awards, Los Angeles फिल्मी Critics संघ, and वेनिस फिल्मी पर्व, and he has दो stars on the हॉलीवुड चलना of Fame.
in 2005, he received the Governors पुरस्कार of the अकादमी of टेलीविज़न Arts & sciences Board of राज्यपालों, जिससे is the highest एमी Award presented.
On February 22, 2009, the अकादमी of Motion Picture Arts और sciences awarded लुईस the Jean Hersholt humanitarian पुरस्कार.
the Rhine ( ; ; ) is a European नदी that runs from the Swiss canton of Grisons in the southeastern Swiss Alps through जर्मनी और eventually बहती into the उत्तर Sea coast in the नीदरलैंड्स और is the twelfth longest नदी in Europe, at परिचय, साथ an औसत discharge of more than.
the राइन और the डेन्यूब formed सबसे of the उत्तरी अंतर्देशीय frontier of the रोमन साम्राज्य and, since those days, the Rhine has महरूम a vital और navigable waterway carrying trade और goods deep अंतर्देशीय.
it रै also served as a defensive feature and has महरूम the basis for क्षेत्रीय and अंतरराष्ट्रीय सीमायें.
the अनेक castles and प्रागैतिहासिक fortifications साथ the राइन गवाही to इसके महत्व as a waterway.
River ट्रैफ़िक could be stopped at these locations, usually for the purpose of collecting tolls, by the राज्य that controlled कि portion of the नदी.
श्री ( सिंहली )
Sri ( Devanagari : श्री, iast ; śrī ), also transliterated as Sree or Shri or श्री is a शब्द of संस्कृत उत्पत्ति, प्रयुक्त in the भारतीय उपमहाद्वीप as polite रूप of address समतुल्य to the अंग्रेज़ी `` mr. '' in written और बोला भाषा, or as a title of veneration लिये deities ( usually अनूदित as `` Holy '' ).
डिज़ाइन of जटिल structures जैसे the अंतरराष्ट्रीय Space Station needs in-depth understanding of Structural Analysis.
Civil अभियान्त्रिकी is a पेशेवर अभियान्त्रिकी अनुशासन that सौदे with the design, construction, and maintenance of the शारीरिक and naturally built environment, सहित works जैसे सड़कें, पुलों, नहरों, dams, and इमारतें.
सिविल अभियान्त्रिकी is the oldest engineering discipline after सैन्य अभियान्त्रिकी, and it थी defined to फर्क non-military engineering इससे सैन्य engineering.
It is traditionally broken into several sub-disciplines सहित पर्यावरणीय अभियान्त्रिकी, भूतकनीकी engineering, भूभौतिकी, भूगणित, कंट्रोल engineering, संरचनात्मक अभियान्त्रिकी, biomechanics, nanotechnology, परिवहन अभियान्त्रिकी, धरती विज्ञान, वायुमंडलीय sciences, forensic अभियान्त्रिकी, municipal or urban engineering, जल resources engineering, materials अभियान्त्रिकी, coastal अभियान्त्रिकी, surveying, और निर्माण अभियान्त्रिकी.
सिविल अभियान्त्रिकी takes प्लेस on all स्तर : in the पब्लिक sector इससे नगरपालिका through to नेशनल सरकारें, and in the private सेक्टर इससे व्यक्तिगत homeowners through to अंतरराष्ट्रीय companies.

Katherine Dunham ( जून 22, 1909 – may 21, 2006 ) थी an अमरीकी नर्तकी, choreographer, author, educator, और social activist.
dunham था एक of the most successful नृत्य careers in अमरीकी और यूरोपीय थिएटर of the 20th century, and निर्देशित उसके अपना नृत्य company for अनेक सालो.
She रै been called the `` matriarch और महारानी mother of ब्लैक नृत्य ''.
दौरान her heyday in the 1940s और 1950s, Dunham was प्रसिद्ध throughout यूरोपीय और लैटिन अमेरिका and was widely popular in the United राज्य, जहाँ the Washington Post पुकारा her `` नर्तकी कैथरीन the Great ''.
लिये almost तीस सालो she कायम the कैथरीन dunham नृत्य कम्पनी, the only self-supported American black dance troupe at कि समय, and over उसके long करियर she choreographed more than ninety individual dances.
dunham was an innovator in African-American आधुनिक नृत्य as खूब as a नेता in the field of dance मानवशास्त्र, or ethnochoreology.
Sphagnum is a genus of between 1510 और 3500 species of mosses, commonly called peat moss due to इसके prevalence in गीला habitats जहाँ it contributes to the formation of peat bogs and mires.
Sphagnum accumulations can store जल, चूंकि दोनो living और dead पौधे can hold large quantities of water अंदर उनके cells ; पौधे may थाम from 16-26 times as much जल as their dry weight depending on the प्रजाति.
the खाली cells सहायता retain जल in drier conditions.
Hence, as sphagnum मॉस grows, it can slowly स्प्रेड into drier शर्तें, forming larger peatlands, दोनो उठाया bogs and कंबल bogs.
ये peat accumulations तब provide आवास लिये a चौड़ी सरणी of peatland पौधे, सहित sedges और ericaceous shrubs, as खूब as orchids और carnivorous पौधे.
sphagnum और the peat formed from it do not decay readily because of the phenolic यौगिकों अंतःस्थापित in the मॉस 's कोशिका walls.
In addition, bogs, जैसे all wetlands, develop अवायवीय soil शर्तें, जिससे produces धीमा अवायवीय क्षय rather than aerobic सूक्ष्मजैविक action.
Peat moss can भी acidify इसके surroundings by लेने up cations, such as कैल्सियम and मैग्नीशियम, और releasing hydrogen ions.
Under the सही शर्तें, peat can accumulate to a depth of अनेक मीटर.
अलग प्रजाति of sphagnum have different tolerance हद लिये बाढ़ and pH, so कोई एक peatland may have a क्रमांक of अलग Sphagnum species.
व्यक्तिगत peat मॉस पौधे consist of a प्रमुख stem, with tightly arranged क्लस्टर of शाखा fascicles usually consisting of दो or three spreading branches और two to चार फांसी शाखाओं.
the top of the संयंत्र, or capitulum, has compact clusters of यंग शाखाओं.
Along the स्टेम are scattered leaves of विभिन्न shapes, named स्टेम leaves ; the shape varies according to species.
the पत्ते consist of दो kinds of कोशिकाएं ; छोटी, ग्रीन, जीना कोशिकाएं ( chlorophyllose cells ), और large, clear, संरचनात्मक, मुर्दे कोशिकाएं ( hyaline कोशिकाएं ).
the latter have the विशाल water-holding capacity.

the संयुक्त Nations ( un ; French : Organisation des राष्ट्र unies, ONU ) is the world 's largest, foremost, और सबसे prominent अंतरराष्ट्रीय organization.
The stated aims of the संयुक्त Nations शामिल promoting and facilitating cooperation in अंतरराष्ट्रीय विधि, अंतरराष्ट्रीय सुरक्षा, आर्थिक विकास, सोशल प्रगति, इंसान अधिकारों, civil rights, सिविल लिबर्टीज, राजनैतिक freedoms, democracy, और the उपलब्धि of lasting संसार peace.
the un was संस्थापित in 1945 after World War ii to replace the लीग of राष्ट्र, to stop युद्धों between देशों, और to provide a मंच for संवाद.

at इसके founding, the UN था 51 member राज्य ; as of 2011, there हैं 193.
इससे इसके offices around the संसार, the un and इसके specialized agencies decide on सत्य and administrative मुद्दे in नियमित meetings held throughout the साल.
the organization has six principal organs : the सामान्य सभा ( the main deliberative सभा ) ; the Security परिषद ( for deciding निश्चित resolutions लिये सलाम और सुरक्षा ) ; the आर्थिक और सोशल परिषद ( लिये assisting in promoting अंतरराष्ट्रीय आर्थिक and social सहयोग and विकास ) ; the Secretariat ( लिये providing अध्ययन, information, and सुविधाएं needed by the un ) ; the International अदालत of Justice ( the primary न्यायिक अंग ) ; और the संयुक्त राष्ट्र Trusteeship Council ( जिससे is currently निष्क्रिय ).
अन्य prominent UN प्रणाली एजेंसियों include the World Health Organization ( WHO ), the संसार खाना कार्यक्रम ( wfp ) और United Nations children 's Fund ( UNICEF ).

the संयुक्त राज्य presidential चुनाव of 1960 was the 44th quadrennial अध्यक्षीय चुनाव, held on मंगलवार, November 8, 1960.
The Republican पार्टी मनोनीत incumbent Vice-President रिचर्ड निक्सन, while the लोकतांत्रिक पार्टी nominated जॉन F. Kennedy, सीनेटर इससे मैसाचुसेट्स.
the लाज़िम अध्यक्ष, Republican ड्वाइट D. आइज़नहावर, थी not eligible लिये re-election बाद serving the maximum दो शर्तें allowed by the twenty-second amendment.
Kennedy was elected साथ a सीसे of 112,827 मत, or 0.17 % of the लोकप्रिय vote, giving उसे a victory of 303 to 219 in the Electoral College, the closest चूंकि 1916.
This थी the पहला election in जिससे all पचास of the current संयुक्त States participated.
a क्रमांक of कारकों बताइये क्यों the चुनाव थी so close.
Kennedy gained since there थी an आर्थिक मंदी जिससे hurt the लाज़िम रिपब्लिकन, और he had the लाभ of 17 लाख अधिक पंजीकृत डेमोक्रेट than republicans.
furthermore, the new मत कि कैनेडी gained among catholics almost neutralized the new मत Nixon gained among protestants.
कैनेडी 's campaigning skills decisively outmatched निक्सन 's.
in the समाप्त, निक्सन 's emphasis on उसके experience carried छोटी वज़न, and he wasted energy by campaigning in सब 50 राज्य instead of concentrating on the झूले राज्य.
कैनेडी प्रयुक्त his विशाल, well-funded campaign organization to जीत the नामांकन, सुरक्षित endorsements, and, साथ the सहायता of the last of the big-city bosses, to मिलेंगी आउट the vote in the big cities.
he relied on कार्यशील mate lyndon B. Johnson to hold the South and प्रयुक्त टेलीविज़न effectively.
इस election is notable as being the first time in u.S. इतिहास that दो sitting u.s. Macbeth is a खेल written by William शेक्सपियर.
It is considered one of his darkest और सबसे शक्तिशाली tragedies.
नियत in Scotland, the play dramatizes the corroding मनोवैज्ञानिक और राजनैतिक effects उत्पादित जब its protagonist, the स्कॉटिश रब मैकबेथ, chooses evil as the रास्ता to fulfill his ambition लिये शक्ति.
he commits regicide to become किंग और तब furthers उसके moral descent साथ a शासनकाल of murderous terror to stay in शक्ति, आखिरकार plunging the country into civil युद्ध.
In the समाप्त, he loses everything कि देता meaning और purpose to his जीवन पहले losing उसके जीवन itself.
The खेल is believed to have been लिखा between 1603 और 1607, और is सबसे commonly दिनाँक 1606.
the earliest account of a प्रदर्शन of what थी probably शेक्सपियर 's play is अप्रैल 1611, when Simon forman अंकित seeing ऐसे a खेल at the Globe थिएटर.
It थी first प्रकाशित in the Folio of 1623, संभवतः इससे a संकेत किताब.
It was सबसे संभावित written दौरान the शासनकाल of James I, जो था महरूम जेम्स VI of स्कॉटलैंड पहले he succeeded to the अंग्रेज़ी throne in 1603.
जेम्स was a संरक्षक of Shakespeare’s एक्टिंग कम्पनी, and of सब the plays Shakespeare लिखा दौरान James’s reign, मैकबेथ most clearly reflects the playwright’s relationship साथ the sovereign.
मैकबेथ is shakespeare’s shortest त्रासदी, और tells the story of a वीर Scottish general नामित Macbeth जो receives a prophecy from a trio of witches कि एक दिन he होगा become किंग of स्कॉटलैंड.
खपत by ambition and spurred to कार्रवाई by his wife, Macbeth murders King डंकन और takes the सिंहासन लिये himself.
उसके शासनकाल is racked साथ guilt and paranoia, and he soon becomes a tyrannical शासक as he is मजबूर to कमिट more और more हत्याएं to protect खुद इससे enmity and suspicion.
The bloodbath swiftly takes Macbeth और Lady मैकबेथ into realms of arrogance, madness, and मौत.
शेक्सपियर 's source लिये the त्रासदी is the खाता of King मैकबेथ of Scotland, macduff, और Duncan in Holinshed 's क्रॉनिकल्स ( 1587 ), a history of England, स्कॉटलैंड and Ireland familiar to Shakespeare और उसके contemporaries, although the कार्यक्रम in the play differ extensively इससे the history of the real मैकबेथ.
In the बैकस्टेज world of theatre, some believe that the खेल is शापित, and होगा नहीं जिक्र इसके title aloud, referring to it instead as `` the स्कॉटिश खेल ``.
over the कोर्स of अनेक सदियां, the play रै attracted some of the सबसे प्रसिद्ध अभिनेताओं to the roles of मैकबेथ and महिला मैकबेथ.
it रै been adapted to film, टेलीविज़न, opera, novels, कॉमिक किताबे, और other media.
the मिल्टन Hershey School is a private philanthropic ( pre-K through 12 ) boarding school in hershey, पेन्सिलवेनिया.
Originally नामित the Hershey औद्योगिक School, the institution was संस्थापित and funded by चॉकलेट उद्योगपति मिल्टन snavely Hershey और उसके wife, Catherine Sweeney Hershey.

With over six अरब डॉलर in एसेट, the मिल्टन hershey School is one of the wealthiest स्कूलों in the world.

The नियंत्रित substances अधिनियम ( सीएसए ) थी enacted into विधि by the कॉंग्रेस of the संयुक्त राज्य as Title II of the Comprehensive ड्रग गाली Prevention और कंट्रोल अधिनियम of 1970.
the CSA is the संघीय u.S. ड्रग policy under जिससे the manufacture, importation, कब्ज़ा, उपयोग and distribution of निश्चित substances is regulated.
The अधिनियम भी served as the नेशनल implementing विधान लिये the सिंगल सम्मेलन on narcotic Drugs.
the विधान निर्मित पाँच Schedules ( classifications ), साथ varying योग्यता लिये a पदार्थ to be included in प्रत्येक.
Two federal एजेंसियों, the Drug Enforcement Administration और the Food and ड्रग प्रशासन, determine जिससे substances हैं added to or removed from the various schedules, हालांकि the statute passed by Congress निर्मित the initial listing, और Congress रै sometimes अनुसूचित अन्य substances through legislation such as the Hillory J. Farias and Samantha Reid date-rape रोकथाम अधिनियम of 2000, जिससे placed gamma hydroxybutyrate in Schedule i. Classification decisions हैं जरूरी to be made on मापदण्ड सहित संभावित for abuse ( an अपरिभाषित पद ), currently accepted चिकित्सा use in treatment in the संयुक्त States, and international treaties.
Second-language acquisition or second-language सीखना is the प्रक्रम by which लोगों learn a second भाषा.
Second-language acquisition ( प्रायः abbreviated to sla ) also refers to the scientific अनुशासन devoted to अध्ययन that process.
दूसरी भाषा refers to any language सीखे in addition to a व्यक्ति 's first language ; हालांकि the concept is नामित second-language acquisition, it can also चरितार्थ the learning of third, चौथी, or subsequent भाषाएं.
second-language acquisition refers to what learners do ; it करता नहीं refer to practices in भाषा teaching.
The अकादमिक discipline of second-language acquisition is a subdiscipline of लागू भाषाविज्ञान.
It is broad-based and relatively नई.
as खूब as the विभिन्न शाखाओं of linguistics, second-language acquisition is भी closely related to मनोविज्ञान, संज्ञानात्मक psychology, and शिक्षा.
to पृथक the अकादमिक discipline इससे the learning process itself, the terms second-language अधिग्रहण शोध, second-language studies, और second-language अधिग्रहण studies हैं भी used.
SLA शोध began as an interdisciplinary field, and क्युकी of इस it is मुश्किल to पहचानो a precise starting date.
however, it does appear to have विकसित a great सौदे चूंकि the mid-1960s.
The term अधिग्रहण was originally प्रयुक्त to emphasize the अवचेतन प्रकृति of the सीखना प्रक्रम, लकिन in हाल सालो सीखना और अधिग्रहण have become largely synonymous.
second-language अधिग्रहण can चरितार्थ विरासत language सीखना, but it does नहीं usually चरितार्थ bilingualism.
सबसे sla शोधकर्ताओं देखिए bilingualism as being the समाप्त result of learning a language, नहीं the process itself, और देखिए the पद as referring to native-like fluency.
लेखक in fields such as शिक्षा और मनोविज्ञान, however, प्रायः use bilingualism loosely to refer to all फ़ॉर्म of बहुभाषिकता.
Second-language अधिग्रहण is भी नहीं to be contrasted साथ the acquisition of a विदेशी भाषा ; बल्कि, the सीखना of second languages and the learning of foreign भाषाएं involve the वही आधारभूत प्रक्रियाओं in अलग हालातs..
वहीँ has महरूम much debate about exactly कैसा भाषा is सीखे, और अनेक मुद्दे are स्टिल unresolved.
There are अनेक theories of second-language अधिग्रहण, लकिन none are accepted as a पूरा explanation by सब SLA researchers.
due to the interdisciplinary nature of the फ़ील्ड of second-language acquisition, इस is नहीं expected to happen in the foreseeable भविष्य.

the list तभी represents प्रत्येक person 's valuation on a single day, due to रोज़ fluctuations among exchange rates और भण्डार valuations.
the संयुक्त राज्य रहस्य Service is a u.S. federal विधि enforcement एजेंसी कि is भाग of the संयुक्त राज्य Department of Homeland Security.
The sworn members are विभाजित among the खास एजेंटों and the uniformed प्रभाग.
Until March 1, 2003, the Service was part of the संयुक्त राज्य विभाग of the राजकोष.
The u.S. रहस्य सेवा रै two distinct क्षेत्रों of responsibility:
Financial Crimes, covering मिशन such as रोकथाम और छानबीन of counterfeiting of U.S. currency और U.S. राजकोष securities, और छानबीन of प्रमुख fraud.
सुरक्षा, which entails ensuring the सुरक्षा of वर्तमान और former नेशनल नेताओ and their परिवारों, ऐसे as the President, पास्ट presidents, वाइस presidents, presidential उम्मीदवार, visiting heads of राज्य, and विदेशी embassies ( per an agreement साथ the u.S. State Department 's Bureau of राजनयिक सुरक्षा ( DS ) दफ्तर of विदेशी मिशन ( ofm ), इत्यादि. )
the Secret सेवा 's आरंभिक responsibility was to investigate counterfeiting of u.S. करेंसी, जिससे थी अनियंत्रित following the U.S. सिविल War.
the agency then evolved into the संयुक्त राज्य ' first घरेलू intelligence and counterintelligence एजेंसी.
Many of the agency 's मिशन were later लिया over by subsequent agencies ऐसे as the संघीय ब्यूरो of Investigation ( एफबीआई ), ब्यूरो of Alcohol, तम्बाकू, firearms और Explosives ( ATF ), Immigration और कस्टम Enforcement ( बर्फ ), और आतंरिक Revenue सेवा ( irs ).

फ्रैंकलिन delano रूज़वेल्ट ( or ; जनवरी 30, 1882 – April 12, 1945 ), also known by his आद्याक्षर, fdr, was the 32nd अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य ( 1933–1945 ) and a सेंट्रल फिगर in world कार्यक्रम दौरान the mid-20th सदी, अग्रणी the United राज्य during a समय of worldwide economic depression and कुल युद्ध.
a प्रबल नेता of the लोकतांत्रिक पार्टी और the तभी अमरीकी अध्यक्ष निर्वाचित to more than दो शर्तें, he निर्मित a New Deal Coalition कि realigned American राजनीती बाद 1932, as उसके domestic policies defined अमरीकी liberalism लिये the middle तीसरा of the 20th सदी.
साथ the bouncy लोकप्रिय सोंग `` प्रसन्न दिनों हैं यहाँ again `` as उसके अभियान थीम, FDR defeated incumbent रिपब्लिकन Herbert हूवर in नवम्बर 1932, at the गहराई of the Great अवसाद.
सक्रिय by उसके निजी victory over पोलियो, FDR 's unfailing आशावाद and activism contributed to a नवीकरण of the national spirit.
he worked closely with British Prime मंत्री विंस्टन चर्चिल और Soviet सामान्य Secretary जोसेफ स्टालिन in अग्रणी the allies विरूद्ध जर्मनी and जापानी in World War II, and restoring समृद्धि to the स्वदेश 's economy.
In his पहला सौ दिनों in office, जिससे began March 4, 1933, रूज़वेल्ट पथप्रदर्शन major विधान and issued a profusion of कार्यपालिका आदेश that instituted the New सौदे —a किस्में of कार्यक्रम designed to produce राहत ( government कार्य लिये the बेरोजगार ), रिकवरी ( economic विकास ), और reform ( through विनियमन of वॉल Street, banks और transportation ).
the economy improved rapidly इससे 1933 to 1937, but then relapsed into a गहन मंदी.
The bipartisan Conservative Coalition that formed in 1937 prevented his packing the परम् Court or गुजर any considerable विधान ; it abolished अनेक of the relief कार्यक्रम जब unemployment diminished दौरान World युद्ध II.
सबसे of the regulations on कारोबार यहूद ended about 1975–85, मगर लिये the regulation of Wall गली by the Securities and एक्सचेंज Commission, जिससे still exists.
साथ साथ several smaller कार्यक्रम, major surviving कार्यक्रम शामिल the संघीय जमा बीमे निगम, जिससे थी created in 1933, और सोशल Security, जिससे कॉंग्रेस passed in 1935.
As संसार युद्ध ii loomed बाद 1938, with the जापानी invasion of चीन and the आक्रामकता of नाजी जर्मनी, fdr दिया strong राजनयिक और वित्तीय support to चीन और Great ब्रिटेन, जबकि बाकी officially neutral.
उसके goal थी to make America the `` Arsenal of लोकतंत्र `` which होता सप्लाई munitions to the allies.
in कूच 1941, Roosevelt, with Congressional स्वीकृति, provided lend-lease सहायता to the countries लड़ against नाजी Germany साथ ब्रिटेन.
साथ very दमदार national support, he बना war on जापानी and जर्मनी after the जापानी आक्रमण on पर्ल हार्बर on दिसम्बर 7, 1941, कॉलिंग it a `` तिथि जिससे होगा सजीव in infamy ``.
He पर्यवेक्षित the mobilization of the U.S. economy to support the अलाइड युद्ध प्रयत्न.
as an active सैन्य नेता, रूज़वेल्ट implemented an overall युद्ध strategy on दो fronts कि ended in the शिकस्त of the Axis शक्तियां और the विकास of the world 's पहला अणु bomb.
in 1942 Roosevelt ordered the internment of 100,000 Japanese American नागरिकों.
बेरोजगारी dropped to 2 %, राहत programs largely ended, और the औद्योगिक economy grew rapidly to नई हाइट्स as millions of लोगों स्थानांतरित to नई jobs in युद्ध centers, और 16 लाख men and 300,000 महिलाओं were drafted or volunteered for military service.
Roosevelt dominated the American राजनैतिक झाँकी not only दौरान the बारह सालो of उसके प्रेसिडेंसी, लकिन also for दशकों afterward.
He orchestrated the realignment of voters कि created the पांचवां Party प्रणाली.
FDR 's New सौदे गठबन्धन united मजदूर संघ, बिग नगर मशीने, white ethnics, अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी and ग्रामीण श्वेत Southerners.
he also influenced the later सृष्टि of the United राष्ट्र and bretton Woods.
रूज़वेल्ट is consistently rated by scholars as one of the शीर्ष three U.S. राष्ट्रपतियों, साथ साथ Abraham lincoln और जार्ज वॉशिंगटन.
a liberal डेमोक्रेट, रूज़वेल्ट पारिभाषित his ideological स्थिति as `` a छोटी बाएँ of बीच. ''
मारा Salvatrucha ( commonly abbreviated as MS, मारा, और MS-13 ) is a transnational दण्ड गिरोह that originated in लॉस Angeles and रै spread to other भाग of the संयुक्त States, Canada, मैक्सिको, और सेंट्रल America.
the majority of the गिरोह is ethnically composed of सेंट्रल Americans and active in शहरी और suburban क्षेत्रों.
In the u.S., the ms-13 रै an especially भारी presence in लॉस एंजिल्स County and the San Francisco Bay क्षेत्रफल in उत्तरी कैलिफ़ोर्निया ; the वॉशिंगटन, d.C. metropolitan areas of Fairfax काउंटी, वर्जिनिया, मोंटगोमरी काउंटी, Maryland, and Prince जार्ज 's काउंटी, मेरीलैंड ; long Island, नई यॉर्क ; the बोस्टन, मैसाचुसेट्स area ; शेर्लोट, North कैरोलिना ; और Houston, Texas.
वहीँ is भी a उपस्थिति of ms-13 in टोरंटो, Ontario, कनाडा.
सदस्यों of MS फर्क themselves by टैटू covering the देह and भी often the फेस, as खूब as the use of उनके अपना चिह्न भाषा.
They are बदनाम लिये उनके use of violence और a subcultural moral code that predominantly consists of merciless revenge and cruel retributions.
इस क्रूरता of the विशिष्ट सदस्यों of the `` maras '' or `` mareros '' अर्जित उन्हें a path to be recruited by the sinaloa कार्टेल battling विरूद्ध लॉस zetas in an जारी drug war south of the United राज्य border.
उनके wide-ranging activities have drawn the ध्यान of the एफबीआई and Immigration and कस्टम प्रवर्तन, who have initiated wide-scale छापे विरूद्ध ज्ञात और suspected gang members – netting hundreds of रखवाले आरपार the country.
हड्डियों is an अमरीकी crime comedy-drama टेलीविज़न series कि premiered on the फॉक्स संजाल in the United राज्य on सितंबर 13, 2005.
the दिखाएँ is based on forensic मानवशास्त्र और forensic पुरातत्व, साथ each episode focusing on an एफबीआई मामला file concerning the mystery behind इंसान remains brought by एफबीआई खास एजेंट Seeley Booth ( दाउद boreanaz ) to the forensic anthropologist Dr. Temperance `` हड्डियों '' Brennan ( Emily deschanel ).
the rest of the main cast शामिल michaela conlin, T. J. thyne, eric millegan, tamara Taylor, Jonathan एडम्स, and जॉन फ्रांसिस Daley.

इसके शीर्षक character, Temperance ब्रेनन, is नामित बाद the protagonist of Reichs ' crime अनोखा series.
Conversely, dr. Brennan writes कामयाब रहस्य novels आधारित around a fictional ( in the Bones universe ) forensic anthropologist नामित कैथी reichs.

The दिग्गज पराजित the बिल्स by the स्कोर of 20–19, जीतना their second कभी Super कटोरी.
it is the only सुपर कटोरी decided by one पाइंट.

the खेल is बेहतरीन remembered for Bills placekicker Scott नॉर्वुड 's last-second फ़ील्ड goal attempt जिससे went चौड़ी सही of the uprights, leading to a दिग्गज विजय, and starting a four-game losing streak in the सुपर Bowl for the Bills.

मैल्कम X ( ; May 19, 1925february 21, 1965 ), born मैल्कम Little और भी ज्ञात as el-hajj Malik el-shabazz ( ), थी an African-American मुस्लिम minister और human अधिकारों activist.
To उसके admirers, he थी a साहसी एडवोकेट लिये the अधिकारों of अश्वेतों, a man जो indicted श्वेत America in the harshest शर्तें for इसके crimes विरूद्ध black अमेरिकी.
Detractors अभियुक्त उसे of preaching जातिवाद, black supremacy, and हिंसा.
he has been पुकारा एक of the महानतम and most influential अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी in इतिहास.
मैल्कम x 's father died—killed by श्वेत supremacists, it थी rumored—when he थी young, and at least one of उसके uncles थी lynched.
जब he थी 13, उसके mother थी लगाई in a दिमागी हॉस्पिटल, और he थी placed in a श्रेणी of फोस्टर घरों.
In 1946, at आयु 20, he गई to थाना for तोड़कर and entering.
In थाना, मैल्कम x became a सदस्य of the स्वदेश of islam ; बाद उसके parole in 1952, he quickly rose to become एक of इसके नेताओ.
लिये a दर्जन years, Malcolm X थी the public फेस of the controversial समूह, but मोहभंग साथ Nation of Islam head इलियास Muhammad led उसे to छोड़ the स्वदेश in कूच 1964.
After a काल of travel in Africa and the मध्य ईस्ट, he लौटे to the United राज्य, where he founded मुस्लिम Mosque, Inc. and the Organization of afro-american एकता.
in February 1965, less than a year after leaving the Nation of islam, he थी assassinated by three members of the group.
मैल्कम x 's expressed beliefs बदला substantially over time.
as a प्रवक्ता लिये the स्वदेश of Islam he taught black supremacy and advocated separation of ब्लैक और white अमेरिकी —in कंट्रास्ट to the सिविल rights गति 's emphasis on integration.
After तोड़कर with the स्वदेश of islam in 1964—saying of his संघ साथ it, `` i किया अनेक बाते as a [ ब्लैक ] Muslim कि i 'm sorry for now.
I थी a zombie तब... pointed in a निश्चित दिशा और told to कूच '' —and बनने a Sunni Muslim, he disavowed racism और expressed willingness to work with सिविल अधिकारों leaders, he जारी to emphasize Pan-Africanism, ब्लैक self-determination, और self-defense.

एलिज़ाबेथ II ( एलिज़ाबेथ Alexandra मरियम ; born 21 अप्रैल 1926 ) is the संवैधानिक monarch of 16 sovereign राज्य, ज्ञात as the Commonwealth realms, and their territories और dependencies, और सिर of the 54-member राष्ट्रमंडल of Nations.
She is Supreme Governor of the Church of इंग्लैण्ड और, in some of उसके realms, carries the title of Defender of the आस्था as part of उसके full title.
On her accession on 6 February 1952, Elizabeth became सिर of the राष्ट्रमंडल और queen regnant of seven स्वतंत्र Commonwealth देशों : the संयुक्त Kingdom, Canada, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, New जीलैंड, दक्षिण Africa, Pakistan और ceylon.
इससे 1956 to 1992, the number of her realms varied as territories gained स्वतंत्रता and some realms became republics.
at present, in जोड to the first चार aforementioned countries, Elizabeth is महारानी of जमैका, Barbados, the बहामा, हरा, पापुआ नई गिनी, the सुलेमान Islands, Tuvalu, Saint लूसिया, Saint Vincent और the Grenadines, बेलीज़, अण्टीगुआ and Barbuda और संत किट्स और नेविस.
Her reign of सालो is फिलहाल the second longest लिये a अंग्रेजों monarch ; only महारानी विक्टोरिया has reigned longer at over 63 years.
Elizabeth was born in लंदन and शिक्षित privately at घर.
Her पिता acceded to the सिंहासन as George vi in 1936 on the abdication of उसके bhai Edward VIII, इससे which समय she was the वारिस presumptive.
वो began to undertake पब्लिक कर्तव्य during the दूसरी World युद्ध, in which she परोसा in the auxiliary territorial सेवा.
in 1947, वो शादीशुदा प्रिंस फिलिप, ड्यूक of Edinburgh, with जिसको वो रै चार children : चार्ल्स, Anne, एंड्रयू, and एडवर्ड.
Her राजतिलक सेवा took प्लेस in 1953 and थी the पहला to be televised.
the Queen 's many ऐतिहासिक visits and meetings शामिल a राज्य visit to the Republic of आयरलैंड और reciprocal विज़िट to and इससे the पोप.
the Queen has देखी प्रमुख constitutional परिवर्तन in उसके realms, ऐसे as devolution in the संयुक्त किंगडम and the patriation of the Canadian constitution.
टाइम्स of निजी significance have शामिल the births and marriages of उसके children, the births of her grandchildren, the प्रतिष्ठापन of the Prince of वेल्स, और the celebration of माइलस्टोन ऐसे as उसके Silver, Golden, and डायमंड jubilees in 1977, 2002, and 2012, respectively.
प्रमुख कार्यक्रम in the महारानी 's शासनकाल have शामिल the Troubles in Northern आयरलैंड, the falklands युद्ध, युद्धों with Iraq और the War in अफगानिस्तान.
There have been times of personal विषाद for उसके which शामिल the मौत of उसके पिता at 56, the हत्या of Prince Philip 's uncle, रब माउंटबेटन, the विश्लेषण of उसके children 's marriages in 1992 ( a साल deemed उसके annus horribilis ), the मौत in 1997 of उसके former daughter-in-law, Diana, Princess of Wales, और the deaths of her माँ and sister in 2002.
the Queen has occasionally faced severe press आलोचना of the royal परिवार and republican sentiments, लकिन support for the साम्राज्य और उसके निजी लोकप्रियता remain high.
the 2010 संयुक्त States सीनेट चुनाव in Florida took प्लेस on November 2, 2010 साथ साथ अन्य elections to the संयुक्त राज्य सीनेट in other states as well as all चुनावों to the संयुक्त राज्य House of प्रतिनिधि and various राज्य and लोकल elections.
Republican मार्को Rubio, former Speaker of the Florida हाउस of प्रतिनिधि, defeated स्वतंत्र चार्ली Crist and Democrat kendrick नम्र in a three-way race.

at the time he received many Republican समर्थन, ऐसे as the National रिपब्लिकन senatorial Committee, Martinez, and the 2008 रिपब्लिकन अध्यक्षीय nominee जॉन McCain.
उसके support of the अमरीकी Recovery और reinvestment अधिनियम of 2009 hurt his popularity among conservatives, and candidate मार्को Rubio surged.
in अप्रैल 2010 Crist announced he would drop आउट of the Republican प्राथमिक और run as an स्वतंत्र.

Doha (, ' or ', वस्तुतः : `` the बिग पेड़ '' ) is the capital city of the state of क़तर.
स्तिथ on the coast of the Persian गल्फ,
it had a जनसांख्यिकी of 998,651 in 2008, and is also एक of the municipalities of Qatar.
दोहा is क़तर 's largest नगर, साथ over 60 % of the nation 's जनसांख्यिकी residing in दोहा or इसके surrounding उपनगरों, and is भी the आर्थिक केन्द्र of the country.
दोहा भी serves as the सीट of सरकारी of Qatar, which is शासित by शेख़ हमद bin खलीफा Al थानी.
Doha is घर to the Education City, an क्षेत्रफल devoted to research और शिक्षा.

the city of दोहा held the 2006 एशियाई खेल, which थी the largest एशियाई Games ever आयोजित.
दोहा भी hosted the 2011 Pan Arab Games and सबसे of the games at the 2011 afc एशियाई कप.

The संसार Petroleum Council held the 20th World पेट्रोलियम सम्मेलन in Doha in दिसम्बर 2011.

झुकना निर्माण, झुकना एंटरप्राइज़, or lean उत्पादन, often बस, `` Lean, '' is a उत्पादन अभ्यास कि considers the व्यय of resources लिये any लक्ष्य अन्य than the सृष्टि of मान लिये the end customer to be अपव्यय, और thus a target लिये elimination.
working इससे the perspective of the customer जो consumes a product or सेवा, `` मान '' is पारिभाषित as कोई कार्रवाई or process कि a customer would be willing to अदा लिये.
Essentially, झुकना is centered on preserving value with कम work.
झुकना निर्माण is a management दर्शनशास्त्र निकला mostly from the Toyota उत्पादन System ( TPS ) ( hence the पद toyotism is also prevalent ) and identified as `` झुकना '' तभी in the 1990s.
TPS is renowned लिये इसके फ़ोकस on कटौती of the असली Toyota सात wastes to improve overall customer value, लकिन वहीँ हैं varying perspectives on कैसा this is best achieved.
the स्थिर विकास of टोयोटा, इससे a छोटी कम्पनी to the संसार 's largest automaker, रै केन्द्रित ध्यान on how it रै achieved this कामयाबी.

a total of 7 seasons और 109 episodes यहूद ब्रॉडकास्ट.
The largest audience of the श्रेणी थी 11.2 लाख दर्शक, with the खास episode `` isaved अपना जीवन '' premiered in January 2010.
जब Carly ( Miranda cosgrove ) और उसके sassy बेहतरीन dost sam ( Jennette mccurdy ) अधिनियम funny at a school talent show ऑडिशन, tech-savvy Freddie ( Nathan kress ) टेपों it और पोस्ट it online बगैर telling उन्हें.

जबकि grappling with typical issues of adolescence, कार्ली, sam, और Freddie ढूँढें out that they have भी become online हस्तियाँ as their दिखाएँ – जिससे सुविधाएँ हुनर प्रतियोगिताओं, recipes, problem-solving, and random नाचना – garners अंतरराष्ट्रीय accolades.
Carly lives in Seattle, वॉशिंगटन साथ उसके 26-year-old bhai और guardian स्पेंसर ( जेरी trainor ) और produces the दिखाएँ in a makeshift third-floor studio मचान in their apartment.
Their माँ has never been देखी or उल्लेखित, but their father, स्टीवन शे ( दाउद chisum ), is a U.S. एयर Force अधिकारी temporarily stationed on a पनडुब्बी, और is often उल्लेखित लकिन is only देखी in person during the श्रेणी finale episode, `` igoodbye ''.
Westlife यहूद an आयरिश लड़के बैंड जिससे formed in 1998 और disbanded in 2012.
originally हस्ताक्षरित by साइमन cowell और managed by लुई वाल्श, the group 's final line-up consisted of nicky Byrne, Kian egan, चिह्नित feehily and शेन filan.
Brian mcfadden थी a सदस्य इससे 1998 जबतक उसके departure in 2004.
westlife बेची over 50 million records विश्वव्यापी, a कुल that included स्टुडियो एल्बम, singles, वीडियो रिलीज, और संकलन एल्बम.
The group संचित 14 number-one singles in the United किंगडम ( the third-highest in UK history ), tying साथ चट्टान रिचर्ड और रैंकिंग बस पीछे the Beatles और Elvis प्रेस्ली.
They achieved a कुल of 26 शीर्ष ten singles over उनके 14-year करियर.
by 2010, westlife was सूचीबद्ध in the गिनीज संसार Records, as the UK 's top-selling एल्बम समूह of the 21st century.
They also won the रिकार्ड of the Year ( the तभी music पुरस्कार based on पब्लिक votes in the uk ) a record-breaking चार टाइम्स और in 2012, the Official चार्ट Company listed westlife 34th amongst the biggest-selling singles artists in British music इतिहास.

in अक्तूबर 2011, westlife घोषित उनके इरादे to विभाजित in 2012, following their महानतम हिट्स Tour and the रिलीज of their महानतम हिट्स album.

Vitamin A is a group of nutritionally असंतृप्त hydrocarbons, जिससे शामिल retinol, retinal, retinoic एसिड and अनेक provitamin a carotenoids among जिससे beta-carotene is the most महत्वपूर्ण.
विटामिन a has multiple कृत्यों, it is important for growth और विकास, लिये the मेंटेनेंस of the immune प्रणाली और शुभ vision.
विटामिन a is needed by the retina of the नजर in the रूप of retinal, which combines साथ प्रोटीन opsin to form rhodopsin the light-absorbing अणु, कि is जरुरी लिये दोनो low-light ( scotopic दृष्टि ) और रंग vision.
विटामिन a भी कृत्यों in a बहुत different भूमिका as an irreversibly oxidized form of retinol ज्ञात as retinoic एसिड, which is an महत्वपूर्ण hormone-like growth फ़ैक्टर for epithelial और अन्य कोशिकाएं.
In foods of animal उत्पत्ति, the major form of विटामिन a is an ester, primarily retinyl palmitate, which is परिवर्तित to रेटिनॉल ( chemically an alcohol ) in the छोटी intestine.
the रेटिनॉल form कृत्यों as a storage form of the विटामिन, और can be converted to and इससे इसके visually active सुव्युद रूप, retinal.
the संबद्ध एसिड ( retinoic acid ), a metabolite कि can be irreversibly synthesized from vitamin A, has only partial vitamin A कार्यकलाप, और does नहीं फलन in the retina लिये the विज़ुअल cycle.
Retinoic एसिड is प्रयुक्त लिये विकास और सेल्यूलर differentiation.
सब फ़ॉर्म of vitamin A have a beta-ionone रिंग to which an isoprenoid chain is attached, called a retinyl group.
दोनो structural सुविधाएँ हैं अनिवार्य लिये vitamin activity.
the नारंगी रंजक of carrots – beta-carotene – can be represented as दो connected retinyl groups, जिससे are used in the देह to contribute to vitamin a स्तर.
alpha-carotene और gamma-carotene भी have a single retinyl समूह, जिससे दे उन्हें some विटामिन activity.
none of the अन्य carotenes have विटामिन कार्यकलाप.
The carotenoid beta- cryptoxanthin possesses an ionone समूह और has vitamin activity in humans.
Vitamin A can be found in two principal forms in भोजन :
Retinol, the form of विटामिन A absorbed when खाने एनिमल food स्त्रोत, is a पीला, fat-soluble substance.
चूंकि the pure दारू रूप is unstable, the vitamin is found in ऊतकों in a form of retinyl ester.
it is भी commercially उत्पादित और administered as esters such as retinyl acetate or palmitate.
the carotenes alpha-carotene, beta-carotene, gamma-carotene ; और the xanthophyll beta-cryptoxanthin ( all of जिससे contain beta-ionone बजती ), लकिन no other carotenoids, function as provitamin A in herbivores and omnivore पशु, जिससे possess the एंजाइम ( 15-15'-dioxygenase ) जिससे cleaves beta-carotene in the intestinal mucosa और converts it retinol.
In general, carnivores are ग़रीब converters of ionine-containing carotenoids, और pure carnivores ऐसे as बिल्लियों और ferrets lack 15-15'-dioxygenase और can नहीं convert any carotenoids to retinal ( resulting in none of the carotenoids होने फ़ॉर्म of vitamin a for ये प्रजाति ).
Selena मारी Gomez ( born July 22, 1992 ) is an American singer और actress.
वो बना her डेब्यू as a child अभिनेत्री in Barney & Friends.
in 2007, गोमेज़ came to prominence as a starring डाल सदस्य in the टेलीविज़न श्रेणी wizards of waverly प्लेस.
She signed to हॉलीवुड Records the following साल, और became the founder और lead सिंगर of the पॉप बैंड सेलिना Gomez & the झाँकी.
Their स्टुडियो albums चुंबन & Tell ( 2009 ), A Year बगैर Rain ( 2010 ), and जब the Sun goes bas ( 2011 ) were certified सुनहरा by the रिकॉर्डिंग उद्योग संघ of America ( RIAA ) और have शाखित platinum-certified singles `` Naturally ``, `` Who says ``, and `` प्रेम तुम जैसे a Love Song ``.
After the release of टेलीविज़न films और उनके accompanying soundtracks, गोमेज़ बना her नाट्य फिल्मी डेब्यू in Ramona and Beezus in 2010 और starred in मोंटे कार्लो in 2011.

sacramento is the capital नगर of the u.S. राज्य of California और the सीट of सरकारी of Sacramento काउंटी.
it is स्तिथ at the confluence of the sacramento नदी और the American नदी in the northern portion of California 's expansive Central घाटी.
With an अनुमानित 2011 population of 477,891, it is the sixth-largest नगर in California और the 35th largest city in the संयुक्त States.
sacramento is the कोर सांस्कृतिक and economic बीच of the sacramento महानगर क्षेत्रफल which शामिल seven काउंटी साथ an estimated 2009 जनसांख्यिकी of 2,527,123.
इसके metropolitan क्षेत्रफल is the चौथी largest in California बाद the वृहद Los एंजिल्स क्षेत्रफल, सैन फ्रांसिस्को खाड़ी Area, और the सैन डिएगो महानगर क्षेत्रफल, as खूब as the 25th largest in the United States.
sacramento was cited by Time पत्रिका as America 's most ethnically और racially एकीकृत city in 2002.
Sacramento became a नगर through the efforts of the स्विस अप्रवासी John sutter, Sr., his son जॉन sutter, Jr., and James W. Marshall.
sacramento grew जल्दी thanks to the protection of Sutter 's फोर्ट, which थी established by sutter in 1839.
दौरान the कैलिफ़ोर्निया सुनहरा फटाफट, sacramento was a major वितरण पाइंट, a commercial and agricultural center, और a टर्मिनस for wagon trains, stagecoaches, riverboats, the telegraph, the Pony एक्स्प्रेस, and the First transcontinental रेलरोड.
कैलिफ़ोर्निया State University, Sacramento, अधिक commonly ज्ञात as sacramento State or सैक राज्य, is the largest local विश्वविद्यालयों.
it is एक of the twenty-three campuses of the California State विश्वविद्यालयों प्रणाली.
Drexel University sacramento is स्तिथ in शहर, sacramento.
University of the Pacific 's McGeorge स्कूल of विधि is located in the Oak पार्क पड़ोस.
in जोड, the विश्वविद्यालयों of California, डेविस is स्तिथ in आसपास डेविस, वेस्ट of the पूंजी.
The UC Davis Medical बीच, a world-renowned शोध hospital, is स्तिथ in the city of Sacramento.
मेमोरियल दिन is a United राज्य संघीय holiday जिससे occurs every साल on the फाइनल सोमवार of may.
Memorial Day is a दिन of remembering the men and महिलाओं जो died while सेवारत in the संयुक्त States हथियारबंद शक्तियां.
formerly ज्ञात as सजावट दिन, it originated after the अमरीकी Civil युद्ध to commemorate the संघ और confederate सैनिको जो died in the सिविल युद्ध.
by the 20th सदी Memorial Day था महरूम extended to honor सब अमेरिकी who have died in सब wars.
It typically marks the start of the गर्मियाँ अवकाश season, जबकि मजदूर Day marks इसके समाप्त.
Many लोगों विज़िट कब्रिस्तान और memorials, विशेषकर to honor those जो have died in military सेवा.
Many स्वयंसेवक प्लेस an American ध्वज on प्रत्येक grave in नेशनल कब्रिस्तान.
by the early 20th सदी, मेमोरियल Day was an occasion for अधिक सामान्य expressions of मेमोरी, as लोगों visited the क़ब्रों of their मृतक रिश्तेदारों in church कब्रिस्तान, whether they था served in the सैन्य or नहीं.
it also became a long weekend increasingly devoted to खरीदारी, परिवार gatherings, आतिशबाजी, यात्राएँ to the beach, and नेशनल media कार्यक्रम.
सालाना Decoration दिनों लिये particular कब्रिस्तान हैं आयोजित on a संडे in late वसन्त or early summer in कुछ rural areas of the अमरीकी South, notably in the mountains.
in मामले involving a परिवार graveyard जहाँ रिमोट पूर्वजो as खूब as those जो यहूद deceased अधिक recently are दफ्न, this may लो on the अक्षर of an extended परिवार reunion to जिससे कुछ लोगों सफर hundreds of miles.
लोगों एकत्रित on the designated दिन और put पुष्प on क़ब्रों और renew सम्पर्क साथ kinfolk and अन्य.
वहीँ प्रायः is a धार्मिक service और a `` dinner on the मैदान, '' the परंपरागत पद for a potluck meal in जिससे लोगों प्रयुक्त to spread the बर्तन आउट on चादरें or चौके on the ग्रास.
it is believed that इस अभ्यास began पहले the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध and thus may प्रतिबिंबित the real उत्पत्ति of the `` memorial दिन '' idea.
मेमोरियल दिन is नहीं to be confused with दिग्गजों Day ; Memorial दिन is a दिन of remembering the men and women जो died while serving, while Veterans दिन मनाता the सेवा of all u.S. military दिग्गजों, living or मुर्दे.

Freedom गर्मियाँ ( भी ज्ञात as the मिसिसिपी Summer Project ) was a अभियान in the संयुक्त States शुभारम्भ in जून 1964 to attempt to पंजीकरण as अनेक African अमरीकी मतदाता as possible in Mississippi, जिससे था historically excluded most अश्वेतों from voting.
the project also set up dozens of Freedom Schools, स्वतंत्रता Houses, और जातियाँ centers in small कस्बों throughout मिसिसिपी to aid the local black जनसांख्यिकी.
the project थी व्यवस्थित by the परिषद of federated Organizations ( cofo ), a coalition of the मिसिसिपी शाखाओं of the चार प्रमुख civil rights संगठन ( SNCC, CORE, NAACP and sclc ).
Most of the impetus, leadership, और financing for the गर्मियाँ Project आए from the sncc.

Blues is the नाम given to दोनो a musical form और a music genre कि originated in communities of primarily the `` गहन South `` of the संयुक्त राज्य around the समाप्त of the 19th century इससे spirituals, work गीतों, फ़ील्ड hollers, shouts and chants, and rhymed सरल narrative ballads.
the ब्लूज़ रूप, सर्वव्यापी in जैज़, rhythm और ब्लूज़, and चट्टान and फेंकें is characterized by विशिष्ट कॉर्ड progressions, of जिससे the twelve-bar ब्लूज़ chord progression is the सबसे आम.
the ब्लू टीप कि, for expressive purposes हैं सुंग or played flattened or धीरे bent ( minor 3rd to major 3rd ) in संबंध to the पिच of the प्रमुख scale, हैं भी an महत्वपूर्ण part of the ध्वनि.
The blues genre is based on the ब्लूज़ रूप but possesses अन्य characteristics ऐसे as विशिष्ट गीत, बास लाइनों, और यंत्र.
Blues can be subdivided into अनेक subgenres ranging इससे देश to urban blues that were अधिक or less लोकप्रिय दौरान different periods of the 20th century.
Best known are the Delta, piedmont, Jump, और शिकागो ब्लूज़ styles.
World युद्ध ii चिह्नित the transition from acoustic to इलेक्ट्रिक blues and the प्रगतिशील opening of ब्लूज़ music to a wider audience, विशेषकर white listeners.
In the 1960s and 1970s, a संकर रूप called blues-rock विकसित.
the term `` the blues '' refers to the `` blue शैतानों '', अर्थ वेदना और उदासी ; an जल्दी उपयोग of the पद in this भाव is मिला in George Colman 's one-act तमाशा Blue Devils ( 1798 ).
Though the उपयोग of the phrase in african-american म्यूज़िक may be पुरानी, it रै been attested to चूंकि 1912, जब हार्ट Wand 's `` डलास Blues `` became the पहला स्वत्वाधिकार blues संयोजन.
in गीत the phrase is प्रायः प्रयुक्त to describe a उदास mood.
a क्वार्टर डालर, commonly shortened to क्वार्टर, is a coin लायक 1⁄4 of a United राज्य डालर or 25 cents.
the quarter has महरूम उत्पादित चूंकि 1796.
The चुनाव of 25¢ as a denomination, as opposed to 20¢ which is अधिक आम in अन्य parts of the world, originated साथ the practice of dividing स्पेनी Milled Dollars into eight wedge shaped segments ( cf. `` टुकड़े of आठ `` ).
at एक time `` दो बिट्स ``, i.e. two wedges, प्रत्येक कील an eighth, यूँ a क्वार्टर of the स्पेनी रियल, was a common उपनाम for a quarter.
Day of the मुर्दे ( ) is a Mexican holiday celebrated throughout मैक्सिको and around the संसार in other संस्कृतियों.
the holiday focuses on gatherings of परिवार and मित्रों to दुवा for और remember मित्रों and परिवार members who have died.
It is विशेषकर मनाये in मैक्सिको, जहाँ it is a national holiday, और सब बैंको are closed.
the जश्न takes प्लेस on नवम्बर 1 और 2, in कनेक्शन साथ the कैथोलिक छुट्टियाँ of सब Saints ' दिन और All souls ' Day.
Traditions कनेक्ट with the अवकाश include भवन निजी altars honoring the मृतक using शुगर skulls, marigolds, और the favorite भोजन और पेय of the रजि और visiting graves साथ ये as उपहार.
वे भी leave possessions of the मृतक.

The अवकाश रै स्प्रेड throughout the संसार : In ब्राज़ील, Dia de Finados is a पब्लिक अवकाश कि अनेक brazilians celebrate by visiting कब्रिस्तान and churches.

George वॉशिंगटन ( –, 1799 ) was the पहला अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त States ( 1789–1797 ), the commander-in-chief of the महाद्वीपीय फौज दौरान the अमरीकी क्रांतिकारी War, and one of the founding fathers of the United States.
he presided over the सम्मेलन कि drafted the Constitution, जिससे replaced the आलेख of Confederation और स्थापित the स्थिति of अध्यक्ष.
वॉशिंगटन थी elected अध्यक्ष as the unanimous choice of the 69 निर्वाचक in 1788, and he परोसा दो terms in दफ्तर.
He oversaw the creation of a दमदार, well-financed national सरकारी that कायम neutrality in the wars raging in यूरोपीय, suppressed rebellion, और won acceptance among अमेरिकी of सब types.
उसके नेतृत्व स्टाइल स्थापित अनेक फ़ॉर्म और rituals of government that have महरूम used चूंकि, ऐसे as using a cabinet प्रणाली and delivering an inaugural address.
Further, the शांतिपूर्ण transition इससे उसके presidency to the presidency of John एडम्स established a tradition कि continues into the 21st century.
Washington थी hailed as `` पिता of उसके देश `` भी during his आजीवन.
वॉशिंगटन was born into the प्रांतीय gentry of Colonial Virginia ; his wealthy planter परिवार owned tobacco बागानों और slaves.
After both उसके पिता और older bhai died when he थी यंग, वॉशिंगटन became personally और professionally संलग्न to the शक्तिशाली विलियम फेयरफैक्स, who प्रचारित उसके करियर as a निरीक्षक and soldier.
वॉशिंगटन quickly became a senior officer in the औपनिवेशिक forces during the पहला चरण of the फ्रेंच and Indian युद्ध.
चुनी by the दूसरी महाद्वीपीय कॉंग्रेस in 1775 to be commander-in-chief of the Continental फौज in the American क्रान्ति, वॉशिंगटन प्रबंधित to force the अंग्रेजों आउट of बोस्टन in 1776, but थी defeated and almost captured later कि year when he lost New यॉर्क नगर.
After क्रासिंग the Delaware River in the dead of winter, he पराजित the अंग्रेजों in two लड़ाइयों, retook New जर्सी and लौटी momentum to the patriot cause.
Because of उसके strategy, क्रांतिकारी शक्तियां captured two major अंग्रेजों सेना at साराटोगा in 1777 और Yorktown in 1781.
इतिहासकारों laud वॉशिंगटन for his चयन और supervision of उसके generals, प्रोत्साहन of morale और क्षमता to hold साथ the फौज, coordination साथ the state राज्यपालों and राज्य militia इकाई, relations with कॉंग्रेस और ध्यान to supplies, लोजिस्टिक्स, और training.
in battle, however, Washington थी repeatedly outmaneuvered by अंग्रेजों सेनापतियों साथ larger armies.
After victory had महरूम finalized in 1783, Washington resigned as commander-in-chief बल्कि than seize शक्ति, proving उसके विपक्ष to तानाशाही और his प्रतिबद्धता to अमरीकी republicanism.
असंतुष्ट साथ the weaknesses of the Articles of Confederation, in 1787 वॉशिंगटन presided over the संवैधानिक सम्मेलन कि drafted the United राज्य संविधान.
Elected unanimously as the पहला अध्यक्ष of the United राज्य in 1789, he attempted to लाओ प्रतिद्वंद्वी गिरोहों together to unify the स्वदेश.
He supported सिकंदर हैमिल्टन 's programs to अदा बंद all state and national कर्ज़, to implement an effective कर प्रणाली और to create a national bank ( despite विपक्ष इससे थामस जेफरसन ).
वॉशिंगटन proclaimed the संयुक्त राज्य neutral in the युद्धों raging in यूरोपीय बाद 1793.
He avoided युद्ध with ग्रेट Britain और guaranteed a decade of सलाम और लाभप्रद व्यापार by securing the jay Treaty in 1795, despite intense विपक्ष इससे the Jeffersonians.
हालांकि never officially joining the Federalist Party, he समर्थित इसके programs.
Washington 's Farewell Address थी an influential primer on republican पुण्य और a चेतावनी विरूद्ध partisanship, sectionalism, और involvement in विदेशी wars.
He रिटायर्ड इससे the प्रेसिडेंसी in 1797 और लौटे to his home, माउंट Vernon, and उसके domestic जीवन जहाँ he managed a variety of उद्यमों.
he freed सब his स्लेव by his final will.
Washington had a vision of a great और powerful स्वदेश that होता be निर्मित on रिपब्लिकन lines using federal शक्ति.
he sought to उपयोग the नेशनल government to preserve स्वतंत्रता, improve अवसंरचना, खोलें the western lands, प्रचार कॉमर्स, found a स्थाई पूंजी, reduce क्षेत्रीय तनाव और promote a स्पिरिट of American राष्ट्रवाद.
at उसके death, Washington was eulogized as `` पहला in युद्ध, पहला in सलाम, और पहला in the hearts of उसके देशवासियों '' by Henry Lee.
the Federalists made उसे the symbol of their party लकिन लिये अनेक सालो, the jeffersonians जारी to distrust his influence और विलम्बित भवन the वॉशिंगटन स्मारक.
as the नेता of the पहला कामयाब revolution against a औपनिवेशिक साम्राज्य in संसार इतिहास, वॉशिंगटन became an international icon for मुक्ति and राष्ट्रवाद, विशेषकर in फ़्रांस और लैटिन अमेरिका.

The Budget of the संयुक्त States Government प्रायः begins as the अध्यक्ष 's proposal to the u.S. Congress which अनुशंसा funding स्तर लिये the next fiscal साल, beginning अक्तूबर 1.
however, Congress is the body जरूरी by विधि to pass a बजट annually और to submit the बजट passed by both houses to the अध्यक्ष for हस्ताक्षर.
Congressional निर्णय हैं governed by नियम और विधान regarding the संघीय budget प्रक्रम.
बजट committees set spending हद लिये the House और सीनेट committees और लिये Appropriations subcommittees, जिससे तब स्वीकृति व्यक्तिगत appropriations bills to allocate funding to विभिन्न federal कार्यक्रम.
If Congress fails to pass an annual budget ( as रै महरूम the case चूंकि 2009 ), a series of appropriations बिल्स जरूर be passed as `` रोकें गैप '' उपायों.
After Congress approves an appropriations bill, it is sent to the अध्यक्ष, who may चिह्न it into विधि, or may वीटो it ( as he होता a बजट when passed by the कॉंग्रेस ).
a vetoed विधेयक is sent back to कॉंग्रेस, जिससे can pass it into विधि साथ a two-thirds majority in each chamber.
Congress may भी combine सब or some appropriations bills into an omnibus reconciliation विधेयक.
in जोड, the president may request और the कॉंग्रेस may pass supplemental appropriations bills or आपात supplemental appropriations बिल्स.
Several government agencies provide बजट आंकड़ा और analysis.
These शामिल the सरकारी जवाबदेही दफ्तर ( GAO ), Congressional बजट दफ्तर, the Office of Management and बजट ( OMB ) और the U.S. राजकोष विभाग.
ये एजेंसियों have reported कि the संघीय सरकारी is facing a श्रेणी of important financing challenges.
in the short-run, कर revenues have declined significantly due to a severe recession और कर नीति चुनाव, while expenditures have विस्तारित for wars, unemployment बीमे और other सुरक्षा net बिता.
in the long-run, expenditures related to healthcare programs such as medicare और medicaid are projected to grow तेज़ than the economy overall as the population matures.
नई गिनी ( also, टोक Pisin : niugini, Dutch : Nieuw गिनी, और ; historically : पापुआ ) is the संसार 's second largest द्वीप, after ग्रीनलैंड, covering a land area of 786,000 km2.
स्तिथ in the दक्षिणपश्चिम Pacific Ocean, it lies geographically to the ईस्ट of the Malay Archipelago, साथ जिससे it is sometimes शामिल as part of a वृहद Indo-Australian द्वीपसमूह.
Geologically it is a part of the same tectonic थाली as ऑस्ट्रेलिया.
जब संसार sea स्तर यहूद low, the दो shared shorelines ( जिससे अभी lie 100 to 140 मीटर below sea स्तर ), combining with lands अभी inundated into the tectonic continent of Sahul, भी ज्ञात as वृहद Australia.
the two landmasses became अलग जब the क्षेत्रफल अभी ज्ञात as the Torres Strait flooded बाद the end of the पिछला glacial काल.
anthropologically, नई Guinea is considered part of मॅलानिशिया.
Politically, the western half of the द्वीप comprises two Indonesian प्रांतों : पापुआ and वेस्ट Papua.
the पूर्वी हाफ फ़ॉर्म the मेनलैंड of the देश of पापुआ नई गिनी.
The द्वीप रै a population of परिचय 7.5 लाख, with a very कम population घनत्व of only 8 inh/km2.
नई गिनी is differentiated इससे इसके drier, खुशामद, और कम fertile southern बंटवारा, Australia, by इसके much higher वर्षा और इसके क्रियाशील volcanic geology, with its उच्चतम point, Puncak jaya, reaching an उन्नयन of 4,884 m ( 16,023 ft ).
Yet the two land masses share a similar एनिमल fauna, साथ marsupials, सहित wallabies और possums, and the egg-laying monotreme, the spiny anteater, or echidna.
अन्य than bats and some दो dozen स्वदेशी rodent genera, there हैं no pre-human स्वदेशी placental mammals.
सूअर, अनेक अतिरिक्त प्रजाति of चूहे, and the पूर्वज of the New गिनी Singing Dog यहूद introduced साथ इंसान colonization.
the इंसान presence on the द्वीप तिथियाँ वापस at तनिक 40,000 सालो to the oldest इंसान migrations out of अफ़्रीकी.
शोध indicates कि the highlands were an जल्दी and स्वतंत्र center of कृषि, साथ प्रमाण of सिंचाई going वापस at तनिक 10,000 years.
क्युकी of the time depth of इसके inhabitation और इसके highly fractured लैंडस्केप, an unusually ऊँची number of भाषाएं are spoken on the द्वीप, साथ कुछ 1,000 languages ( a फिगर higher than कि of most महाद्वीपों ) having been catalogued आउट of an अनुमानित world-wide pre-Columbian कुल of 6,000 इंसान dialects.
सबसे हैं classified as पापुआई भाषाएं, a generally स्वीकृत भौगोलिक term जिससे a अल्पसंख्यक of authors थाम to be a जेनेटिक एक.
a number of ऑस्ट्रोनीशियाई भाषाएं हैं spoken on the coast और on offshore आइलैंड्स.
In the 16th century स्पेनी explorers खोजा the द्वीप और called it नुएवा गिनी.
in हाल इतिहास पश्चिमी नई Guinea थी शामिल in the डच East Indies colony.
The germans annexed the northern coast of the पूर्वी हाफ of the द्वीप as German New Guinea in their pre–World युद्ध I प्रयत्न to establish themselves as a colonial शक्ति, whilst the दक्षिण eastern portion was अनिच्छा claimed by ब्रिटेन.
Following the Treaty of versailles, the German portion was awarded to ऑस्ट्रेलिया ( which थी already शासी the अंग्रेजों claim, नामित the Territory of Papua ) as a लीग of Nations जनादेश.
the eastern हाफ of the द्वीप थी granted स्वतंत्रता from Australia as पापुआ नई गिनी in 1975.
the पश्चिमी हाफ gained स्वतंत्रता इससे the डच in 1961, लकिन became भाग of इंडोनेशिया जल्द afterwards in विवादास्पद circumstances.

Bevo चिह्न
bevo थी a non-alcoholic malt beverage, or निकट बियर, brewed in the United राज्य by the Anheuser-Busch कम्पनी beginning in the early 20th century.
Bevo enjoyed इसके महानतम success दौरान the time of prohibition, जब बियर, wine and distilled liquors, यहूद made illegal लिये thirteen years.
the Anheuser-Busch company started brewing Bevo when alcoholic beverages यहूद निषिद्ध in 1916 by the संयुक्त राज्य हथियारबंद शक्तियां.

मोटरसाइकिल स्पीडवे, प्रायः referred to as स्पीडवे, is a मोटरसाइकिल sport involving four and sometimes up to six राइडर्स स्पर्धा over four anti-clockwise laps of an ओवल सर्किट.
Speedway मोटरसाइकिल उपयोग तभी एक gear और have no brakes and रेसिंग takes place on a flat oval track प्रायः consisting of मैल or loosely packed shale.
प्रतिस्पर्धी use this surface to स्लाइड उनके मशीने बगलों, powersliding or broadsiding into the bends.
on the straight भाग of the track the motorcycles reach speeds of up.

विटामिन D is a समूह of fat-soluble secosteroids responsible for intestinal अवशोषण of कैल्सियम और phosphate.
in humans, the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण सम्बन्धित compounds of vitamin d are vitamin d2 और विटामिन d3.
Cholecalciferol ( विटामिन d3 ) और ergocalciferol ( विटामिन D2 ) हैं अद्वितीय as they constitute कया we जान as vitamin D और can be ingested from the diet and/or पूरक.
the देह can also synthesize विटामिन D ( from कोलेस्ट्रॉल ) जब सूर्य exposure is पर्याप्त ( hence its nickname, the `` सनशाइन vitamin '' ).
हालांकि विटामिन d is commonly पुकारा a vitamin, it is नहीं दरअसल an essential dietary vitamin in the strict sense, as it can be synthesized in पर्याप्त amounts by सबसे mammals exposed to धूप.
( Cats and dogs can not synthesize विटामिन D efficiently और must प्राप्त it in उनके आहार. )
An सशुल्क chemical compound ( or सम्बन्धित set of compounds ) is तभी scientifically पुकारा a विटामिन जब it can नहीं be synthesized in sufficient quantities by an सजीव, और जरूर be प्राप्त from उनके diet.
however, as साथ other compounds commonly called विटामिन, vitamin d थी खोजा in an प्रयत्न to find the dietary पदार्थ कि थी lacking in a बीमारी, namely, rickets, the बाल्यकाल form of osteomalacia.
additionally, जैसे other यौगिकों called विटामिन, in the developed world vitamin d is added to staple भोजन, such as milk, to avoid बीमारी due to कमियां.
Measures of serum स्तर reflect endogenous synthesis from एक्सपोज़र to sunlight as खूब as सेवन इससे the diet, और it is believed कि संश्लेषण may योगदान generally to the maintenance of adequate serum concentrations.
The evidence indicates कि the synthesis of vitamin D इससे sun exposure works in a प्रतिक्रिया loop कि prevents toxicity लकिन, because of अनिश्चितता about the cancer risk इससे धूप, no सुझाव हैं जारी by the संस्थान of आयुर्विज्ञान, USA, लिये the राशि of sun exposure जरूरी to मिलें vitamin D आवश्यकताएँ.
तदनुसार, the dietary सन्दर्भ Intakes for विटामिन D assume that no संश्लेषण occurs और कि all of a person 's विटामिन d is from उनके आहार, although that होगा rarely occur in practice.
in the liver विटामिन d is परिवर्तित to calcidiol, which is भी known as calcifediol ( INN ), 25-hydroxycholecalciferol, or 25-hydroxyvitamin d—abbreviated 25 ( OH ) D ; और जिससे is the specific विटामिन D metabolite कि is measured in serum to determine a person 's विटामिन d औकात.
Part of the calcidiol is परिवर्तित by the गुर्दे to calcitriol, the biologically क्रियाशील रूप of विटामिन D. Calcitriol circulates as a हार्मोन in the blood, regulating the concentration of calcium और फास्फेट in the bloodstream और promoting the healthy growth और remodeling of अस्थि.
Calcidiol is भी परिवर्तित to calcitriol बाहर of the गुर्दे लिये other उद्देश्य, ऐसे as the अप्रसार, differentiation and apoptosis of कोशिकाएं ; calcitriol भी affects neuromuscular फलन और सूजन.
परे its उपयोग to prevent osteomalacia or rickets, the प्रमाण लिये अन्य health प्रभाव of विटामिन d supplementation in the general जनसांख्यिकी is inconsistent.

the यहूदियों ( आईएसओ 259-3 israeli उच्चारण ), also known as the यहूदी लोगों, हैं a nation और an ethnoreligious समूह, originating in the Israelites or hebrews of the प्राचीन निकट ईस्ट.
the Jewish नस्ल, राष्ट्रीयता, और धर्म are strongly interrelated, as judaism is the traditional आस्था of the Jewish nation.
converts to Judaism, whose औकात as Jews भीतर the Jewish ethnos is equal to those born into it, have been absorbed into the Jewish people throughout the millennia.
In यहूदी परंपरा, Jewish ancestry is traced to the biblical patriarchs Abraham, Isaac and याक़ूब in the दूसरी millennium BCE.
the modern State of इसराईल was established as a यहूदी nation-state, और defines itself as ऐसे in इसके Basic कानून.
इसके विधि of वापसी अनुदान the right of नागरिकता to कोई jew जो निवेदन it.
Israel is the तभी देश where यहूदियों हैं a बहुमत of the जनसांख्यिकी.
यहूदियों भी enjoyed political autonomy twice पहले in प्राचीन history.
The पहला of these periods lasted from 1350 to 586 bce, और encompassed the periods of the Judges, the संयुक्त Monarchy, and the Divided साम्राज्य of the Kingdoms of इसराईल and यहूदा, समाप्ति साथ the destruction of the First टेम्पल.
the दूसरी थी the काल of the hasmonean किंगडम spanning from 140 to 37 BCE.
Since the destruction of the First टेम्पल, most यहूदियों have जिया in diaspora.
a अल्पसंख्यक in every country in which वे सजीव ( मगर इसराईल ), वे have अक्सर अनुभवी persecution throughout इतिहास, resulting in a जनसांख्यिकी कि रै fluctuated दोनो in संख्याएँ and distribution over the सदियां.
The संसार Jewish population reached a peak of 15 लाख prior to the Second संसार युद्ध, लकिन छह लाख Jews यहूद मारे in the Holocaust.
Since then the जनसांख्यिकी has risen again और, थी estimated at 13.4 लाख by the उत्तर अमरीकी यहूदी आंकड़ा Bank, or कम than 0.2 % of the total world population ( roughly एक in every 514 लोगों ).
According to इस report, about 42.5 % of सब Jews reside in इसराईल ( 5.7 लाख ), और 39.3 % in the United राज्य ( 5.3 लाख ), साथ most of the शेष living in यूरोपीय ( 1.5 million ) and कनाडा ( 0.4 million ).
ये संख्याएँ include सब those who consider themselves यहूदियों, whether or not they हैं संबद्ध साथ a यहूदी संगठन.
the total संसार Jewish population, however, is मुश्किल to माप.

the feast of Corpus Christi ( Latin लिये Body of Christ ), भी ज्ञात as कॉर्पस domini, is a लैटिन रीति liturgical solemnity celebrating the tradition and belief in the देह और blood of Jesus मसीह and उसके रियल उपस्थिति in the Eucharist.
it emphasizes the आनन्द of the संस्था of the Eucharist, जिससे थी observed on Holy Thursday in the somber atmosphere of the nearness of शुभ शुक्रवार.
in the present Roman Missal, the feast is designated the solemnity of The सबसे Holy देह और रक्त of Christ.
It is also मनाये in कुछ anglican, लूथरन, और Old कैथोलिक Churches कि थाम समान beliefs regarding the Real उपस्थिति.
the feast is liturgically मनाये on the Thursday बाद Trinity Sunday or, `` जहाँ the Solemnity of the Most पावन Body and Blood of मसीह is नहीं a Holy दिन of दायित्व, it is assigned to the Sunday बाद the सबसे पावन Trinity as इसके उचित दिन ''.
At the end of पावन द्रव्यमान, there is often a बारात of the धन्य sacrament, generally displayed in a monstrance.
The बारात is followed by सुनाकर of the Blessed Sacrament.
A notable Eucharistic procession is कि presided over by the पोप प्रत्येक साल in Rome, where it begins at the archbasilica of St. जॉन Lateran and makes इसके रास्ता to the basilica of Saint Mary Major, where it concludes साथ सुनाकर.
C-reactive प्रोटीन ( CRP ) is a प्रोटीन मिला in the blood, the स्तर of which वृद्धि in जवाब to inflammation ( i.e. C-reactive प्रोटीन is an acute-phase प्रोटीन ).

CRP is synthesized by the जिगर in response to कारकों released by macrophages और मोटे cells ( adipocytes ).
It is a सदस्य of the pentraxin परिवार of प्रोटीन.
it is नहीं सम्बन्धित to C-peptide or प्रोटीन c.
c-reactive protein थी the पहला पैटर्न मान्यता receptor ( PRR ) to be identified.
the प्रारंभ of the systematic यूरोपीय colonization of the americas is typically दिनाँक to 1492, जब a Spanish expedition headed by क्रिस्टोफर Columbus sailed for इण्डिया to खोलें व्यापार लकिन inadvertently खोजा the Americas.

the पहला रिझाने occurred along the caribbean coasts on the आइलैंड्स of हिस्पानिओला, Puerto रीको और क्यूबा, and बाद 1500 extended into the इंटीरियर्स of both उत्तर and दक्षिण अमेरिका.
In 1497, sailing इससे the उत्तर on निमित्त of इंग्लैण्ड, John cabot landed on the उत्तर अमरीकी coast, और a साल later, Columbus 's third voyage reached the South अमरीकी coast.
फ़्रांस founded colonies in much of eastern उत्तर अमेरिका, on a क्रमांक of caribbean आइलैंड्स, and in दक्षिण अमेरिका.
पुर्तगाल colonized Brazil.
आखिरकार, the संपूर्ण पश्चिमी गोलार्ध came अंतर्गत the control of यूरोपीय सरकारें, अग्रणी to profound परिवर्तन to its landscape, जनसांख्यिकी, and plant and animal जीवन.
in the 19th century अलोन over 50 million लोगों बाएँ यूरोपीय for the Americas.

टेस्टोस्टेरोन is a steroid hormone इससे the androgen समूह और is मिला in स्तनधारियों, सरीसृपों, पक्षियों, and अन्य vertebrates.
In स्तनधारियों, टेस्टोस्टेरोन is primarily secreted in the testicles of males and the अंडाशय of महिलाओं, हालांकि छोटी amounts are भी secreted by the अधिवृक्क glands.

In मेन, टेस्टोस्टेरोन plays a key भूमिका in the विकास of पुरूष reproductive ऊतकों ऐसे as the testis और prostate as खूब as promoting secondary यौन characteristics such as increased muscle, bone द्रव्यमान, और the विकास of देह hair.

महिलाओं also are more संवेदनशील to the hormone.
टेस्टोस्टेरोन is observed in most vertebrates.
मछली make a थोड़ा अलग form called 11-ketotestosterone.
इसके counterpart in कीट is ecdysone.
