Cluster sampling is a sampling तकनीक used when `` प्राकृतिक '' but अपेक्षाकृत समरूप groupings हैं evident in a सांख्यिकीय population.
it is often प्रयुक्त in marketing research.
In इस technique, the total जनसांख्यिकी is विभाजित into ये groups ( or क्लस्टर ) और a सरल यादृच्छिक sample of the समूह is selected.
तब the required सूचना is एकत्रित इससे a सरल random sample of the elements within प्रत्येक selected समूह.
This may be किया लिये प्रत्येक तत्व in these समूह or a subsample of तत्व may be चयनित within each of these समूह.
a common motivation लिये cluster sampling is to reduce the कुल number of साक्षात्कार and लागत दिए the desired accuracy.
assuming a फिक्स्ड नमूना आकार, the तकनीक gives अधिक सटीक results जब सबसे of the विभिन्नता in the population is भीतर the समूह, नहीं between उन्हें.

तांबे is a रासायनिक तत्व साथ the प्रतीक cu ( इससे ) और atomic number 29.
it is a ductile metal with बहुत ऊँची thermal और विद्युत चालकता.
Pure copper is नरम और malleable ; a freshly exposed surface रै a reddish-orange color.
it is प्रयुक्त as a conductor of ऊष्मा और electricity, a building सामग्री, और a constituent of विभिन्न मेटल alloys.
the metal और इसके alloys have been प्रयुक्त लिये thousands of years.
In the रोमन era, copper was प्रधानतया mined on Cyprus, hence the origin of the नाम of the मेटल as сyprium ( मेटल of Cyprus ), बाद shortened to сuprum.
इसके compounds हैं commonly encountered as copper ( II ) salts, जिससे often impart ब्लू or green रंगों to minerals such as azurite और turquoise and have महरूम widely प्रयुक्त historically as pigments.
architectural structures निर्मित with तांबे corrode to give ग्रीन verdigris ( or patina ).
सजावटी आर्ट prominently सुविधाएँ copper, both by itself and as भाग of pigments.
तांबे is essential to all जीना organisms as a ट्रेस dietary खनिज क्युकी it is a key constituent of the respiratory enzyme जटिल cytochrome c oxidase.
In molluscs and crustacea copper is a constituent of the blood रंजक hemocyanin, जिससे is replaced by the iron-complexed hemoglobin in मछली और अन्य vertebrates.
The प्रमुख क्षेत्रों where तांबे is मिला in vertebrates हैं liver, मांसपेशी और अस्थि.
in sufficient concentration, तांबे compounds are जहरीला to higher जीवों और are used as bacteriostatic substances, fungicides, and लकडी preservatives.
The प्रमुख पेशेवर sports लीग, or बस major leagues, in the संयुक्त States and कनाडा हैं the highest पेशेवर competitions of टोली sports in the two countries.
हालांकि व्यक्तिगत खेल ऐसे as गोल्फ़, tennis, and auto racing are भी बहुत लोकप्रिय, the पद is usually सीमित to टोली sports.
The पद `` major league '' थी first used in 1921 in reference to प्रमुख लीग बेसबॉल ( एमएलबी ), the top level of professional अमरीकी बेसबॉल.
Today, the प्रमुख उत्तरी उत्तर America पेशेवर टोली खेल लीग are प्रमुख लीग बेसबॉल ( MLB ), the National बास्केट संघ ( NBA ), the National फ़ुटबॉल लीग ( एनएफएल ), और the नेशनल हॉकी League ( NHL ).
अन्य notable लीग शामिल प्रमुख लीग Soccer ( MLS ), the कनाडाई फ़ुटबॉल League ( cfl ), the एरिना फ़ुटबॉल League, प्रमुख League lacrosse, the नेशनल lacrosse League और the Women 's नेशनल बास्केट Association.
the NFL, एमएलबी, NBA, और एनएचएल are commonly referred to as the बिग चार.
प्रत्येक of ये is the richest पेशेवर क्लबों प्रतियोगिता in इसके sport worldwide.
the best खिलाड़ी can become सांस्कृतिक icons in both देशों और elsewhere in the संसार, because the leagues enjoy a significant प्लेस in popular culture in the us और कनाडा.
the एनएफएल has 32 टीमों, and the अन्य have 30 प्रत्येक.
the vast बहुमत of प्रमुख लीग teams हैं concentrated in the सबसे populous metropolitan क्षेत्रों of the संयुक्त States.
Baseball, football, hockey, और सॉकर have had professional leagues लिये over 100 सालो ; जल्दी लीग such as the नेशनल संघ, ओहियो League, and नेशनल Hockey संघ formed the आधार of the आधुनिक MLB, NFL और NHL क्रमशः.
Soccer थी पहला professionalized in 1894, लकिन leagues suffered greatly इससे कमी of स्थिरता और seldom lasted अधिक than a decade.
सॉकर 's महानतम successes यहूद in the रूप of the अमरीकी सॉकर League ( 1921-1933 ), the असली उत्तर अमरीकी सॉकर लीग ( 1968-1984 ), the National Professional सॉकर लीग ( 1984-2001 ) और, फिलहाल, प्रमुख लीग Soccer ( 1996-present ).
बास्केट is a अपेक्षाकृत new development ; the एनबीए evolved इससे the National बास्केट League और इसके splinter समूह the बास्केट संघ of America, taking on its current रूप in 1949.
प्रत्येक major league averages 15,000 fans in उपस्थिति प्रति खेल or उच्चतर as of 2011.

अर्जित value management ( evm ), or अर्जित मान project/performance प्रबन्धन ( EVPM ) is a project प्रबन्धन तकनीक लिये measuring प्रोजेक्ट प्रदर्शन और प्रगति in an उद्देश्य manner.
क्युकी EVM has the ability to combine माप of :
पैमाना
अनुसूची
and cost,
in a सिंगल एकीकृत प्रणाली, अर्जित मान Management is able to provide सटीक forecasts of प्रोजेक्ट performance problems, which is an महत्वपूर्ण योगदान लिये प्रोजेक्ट प्रबन्धन.
Early EVM शोध दिखाया कि the क्षेत्रों of नियोजन and कंट्रोल हैं significantly impacted by इसके उपयोग ; और similarly, using the methodology improves दोनो scope परिभाषा as well as the विश्लेषण of overall project प्रदर्शन.
अधिक हाल research studies have shown that the सिद्धान्त of evm हैं धनात्मक predictors of प्रोजेक्ट कामयाबी.
लोकप्रियता of evm रै grown significantly in recent years परे सरकारी contracting, in जिससे सेक्टर its importance continues to rise ( e.g., हाल new DFAR rules ), in part क्युकी evm can also सतह in and सहायता substantiate contract disputes.
Colorful spring गार्डन पुष्प
Spring is one of the four conventional शीतोष्ण seasons, following शीत and preceding summer.
वहीँ हैं विभिन्न technical परिभाषाएं of spring, but लोकल उपयोग of the term varies according to local climate, संस्कृतियों और कस्टम.
जब it is spring in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध, it will be autumn in the southern गोलार्ध.
At the वसन्त equinox, दिनों हैं close to 12 घंटों long साथ दिन लंबाई increasing as the ऋतु progresses.
वसन्त और `` springtime '' refer to the season, और भी to ideas of rebirth, कायाकल्प, renewal, क़यामत, और regrowth, साथ त्यौहार ऐसे as Carnival, ईस्टर और Holi होने celebrated at this समय.
Jamestown was a settlement in the उपनिवेश of वर्जिनिया, the पहला permanent अंग्रेज़ी उपनिवेश in the Americas.
स्थापित by the वर्जिनिया कम्पनी of लंदन as `` James Fort '' on May 14, 1607 ( O.S., may 24, 1607 n.s. ), it followed अनेक पहले विफल attempts, including the खोया Colony of roanoke.
Jamestown परोसा as the पूंजी of the उपनिवेश लिये 83 years, from 1616 until 1699.
the उपनिवेश थी स्तिथ भीतर the territory of a राजनैतिक entity ज्ञात as Tsenacommacah, the राज्य of the powhatan Confederacy, with around 14,000 देशी inhabitants, and specifically was in भाग of the subdivision ज्ञात as the paspahegh जनजाति.
the natives initially सत्कार the colonists with नाचना, feasting and tobacco ceremonies, and they provided निर्णायक प्रावधानों और support for the अस्तित्व of the colonists, who यहूद नहीं agriculturally inclined, हालांकि relations साथ the newcomers also soured fairly early on, अग्रणी to the total annihilation of the Paspahegh in warfare भीतर 3 सालो.
भीतर a साल of jamestown 's founding, the Virginia Company brought पॉलिश and Dutch colonists to help improve the उपनिवेश.
In 1619, the पहला प्रलेखित africans यहूद brought to Jamestown, हालांकि the आधुनिक conception of गुलामी in the भविष्य संयुक्त राज्य किया not शुरू in Virginia until 1660.
When the colony was subdivided into the original आठ shires of Virginia in 1634, the town became स्तिथ in the eponymous जेम्स नगर शायर.
the London कम्पनी 's second उपनिवेश, बरमूडा, claims to be the साईट of the oldest कस्बा in the अंग्रेज़ी नई संसार, as St. जार्ज 's, बरमूडा was officially स्थापित ( as New लंदन ) in 1612, whereas जेम्स फोर्ट, in Virginia, थी not to be परिवर्तित into जेम्स towne जबतक 1619, and further did not survive into the उपस्थित दिन.
in 1699, the पूंजी थी relocated इससे Jamestown to कया is today Williamsburg, after which jamestown ceased to मौजूद as a settlement, existing आज तभी as an पुरातत्व site.
आज, jamestown is एक of three locations comprising the Historic Triangle of Colonial वर्जिनिया, साथ with Williamsburg and yorktown, साथ two प्राथमिक heritage sites.
Historic jamestowne, the पुरातत्व site on jamestown Island, is a cooperative effort by jamestown National Historic Site ( part of औपनिवेशिक नेशनल Historical पार्क ), and Preservation वर्जिनिया.
the Jamestown उपनिवेश, a जीना history interpretive site, is संचालित by the Jamestown yorktown Foundation in संयोजन with the राष्ट्रमंडल of Virginia.

Heliocentrism, or heliocentricism, is the astronomical model in which the धरती and planets revolve around a relatively stationary Sun at the बीच of the Solar प्रणाली.
The शब्द आता इससे the यूनानी ( helios `` सूर्य '' and kentron `` center '' ).
historically, heliocentrism थी opposed to geocentrism, जिससे लगाई the धरती at the center.
the notion that the धरती घूमती around the Sun था महरूम proposed as early as the 3rd century bc by aristarchus of samos, लकिन aristarchus 's heliocentrism attracted छोटी attention जबतक कोपरनिकस revived और elaborated it.
लुसियो Russo, however, argues कि इस is a misleading छाप resulting इससे the loss of scientific works of the hellenistic era.
using अप्रत्यक्ष प्रमाण he argues that a heliocentric view थी expounded in हिप्पारकस 's work on गम्भीरता.
It was नहीं जबतक the 16th century कि a fully predictive गणितीय model of a heliocentric system थी presented, by the पुनर्जागरण mathematician, astronomer, and Catholic मौलवी nicolaus कोपरनिकस of Poland, leading to the Copernican क्रान्ति.
in the following सदी, योहानेस कॅप्लर elaborated upon और विस्तारित this मॉडल to शामिल elliptical orbits, and supporting observations बना using a telescope were प्रस्तुत by Galileo Galilei.
With the observations of William हर्शेल, Friedrich bessel, और others, खगोलशास्त्रियों एहसास that the सूर्य थी नहीं the बीच of the ब्रह्मांड and by the 1920s एडविन हबल था दिखाया that it was part of a galaxy ( the Milky Way ) कि थी तभी एक of अनेक अरबों.

For other uses, देखिए आयाम ( बहुविकल्पी ).
From left to सही, the वर्गाकार, the घन, और the tesseract.
the square is bounded by 1-dimensional लाइनों, the घन by 2-dimensional क्षेत्रों, और the tesseract by 3-dimensional आयतन.
A प्रक्षेप of the घन is दिए since it is viewed on a two-dimensional स्क्रीन.
the same applies to the tesseract, जिससे additionally can तभी be दिखाया as a प्रक्षेप भी in three-dimensional स्पेस.
A आरेख showing the पहला चार स्थानिक dimensions.
in physics और mathematics, the आयाम of a स्पेस or object is informally पारिभाषित as the minimum क्रमांक of coordinates needed to बताएँ कोई point within it.
यूँ a लकीर रै a dimension of एक क्युकी only एक निर्देशांक is needed to बताएँ a पाइंट on it ( लिये example, the point at 5 on a क्रमांक लकीर ).
a सतह such as a प्लेन or the surface of a cylinder or गोला रै a dimension of दो क्युकी two निर्देशांक हैं needed to बताएँ a point on it ( लिये उदाहरण, to locate a पाइंट on the surface of a गोला you need दोनो इसके latitude and इसके longitude ).
The अंदर of a cube, a बेलन or a गोला is three-dimensional because तीन निर्देशांक हैं needed to locate a पाइंट भीतर ये स्पेसेस.
in शारीरिक शर्तें, dimension refers to the constituent ढांचा of all space ( volume ) and इसके स्थिति in time ( perceived as a scalar dimension along the t-axis ), as well as the spatial संविधान of वस्तुएँ within—structures that correlate with both particle और फ़ील्ड conceptions, interact according to relative गुण of mass —and हैं fundamentally गणितीय in वर्णन.
These, or other अक्ष, may be referenced to uniquely पहचानो a पाइंट or ढांचा in its attitude और संबंध to अन्य वस्तुएँ and आवृत्ति.
Physical theories that incorporate समय, such as सामान्य आपेक्षिकता, हैं कहा to work in 4-dimensional `` spacetime ``, ( पारिभाषित as a मिन्कोवस्की स्पेस ).
आधुनिक theories tend to be `` higher-dimensional '' सहित क्वांटम फ़ील्ड और स्ट्रिंग theories.
The state-space of quantum यांत्रिकी is an infinite-dimensional function space.
The concept of आयाम is नहीं प्रतिबंधित to शारीरिक objects.
High-dimensional स्पेसेस occur in mathematics and the sciences लिये अनेक reasons, अक्सर as configuration स्पेसेस ऐसे as in Lagrangian or Hamiltonian यांत्रिकी ; ये are abstract स्पेसेस, स्वतंत्र of the शारीरिक स्पेस we live in.

Canadian historians until the 1980s tended to फ़ोकस on economic history, including labour history.
in भाग इस is क्युकी Canada has had far कम political or military conflicts than अन्य समाजों.
इस was especially सच्चा in the first half of the twentieth सदी जब आर्थिक इतिहास थी overwhelmingly प्रबल.
अनेक of the सबसे prominent अंग्रेज़ी कनाडाई इतिहासकारों इससे इस period were आर्थिक इतिहासकारों, ऐसे as हेरोल्ड innis, Donald Creighton और आर्थर R. M. Lower
विद्वानों of Canadian इतिहास were heirs to the परंपराओं that विकसित in यूरोपीय और the United States, लकिन frameworks that worked खूब elsewhere प्रायः विफल in कनाडा.
The heavily मार्क्सवादी बहकावे economic इतिहास कि dominates यूरोपीय रै छोटी प्रासंगिकता to सबसे of Canadian history.
a focus on क्लास, शहरी areas, and उद्योग fails to पता कनाडा 's ग्रामीण और संसाधन based अर्थव्यवस्था.
similarly, the monetarist school कि is प्रबल in the United राज्य भी रै been मुश्किल to ट्रांसफ़र उत्तर of the किनारा.
the पढ़ाई of economic history in कनाडा became highly केन्द्रित on आर्थिक भूगोल, and लिये many सालो the प्रबल school of thought रै been the स्टेपल्स लेख.
इस school of विचार bases the पढ़ाई of the Canadian अर्थव्यवस्था on the पढ़ाई of natural संसाधन.
This approach रै चूंकि also become प्रयुक्त बाहर of Canada in ऑस्ट्रेलिया और in अनेक developing राष्ट्र.
पहले the आगमन of europeans, the पहला Nations of what होता become Canada था a विशाल and vibrant trade संजाल.
Furs, टूल्स, decorative items, और अन्य goods were प्रायः transported thousands of kilometres, mostly by canoe throughout the अनेक rivers और lakes of the प्रदेश.
the जल्दी यूरोपीय इतिहास of the Canadian अर्थव्यवस्था is usually studied through the स्टेपल्स thesis which argues the Canadian अर्थव्यवस्था विकसित through the exploitation of a series of staples कि would be exported to Europe.
carbon-14, 14c, or radiocarbon, is a radioactive समस्थानिक of कार्बन with a केंद्रक containing 6 protons and 8 neutrons.
इसके उपस्थिति in organic materials is the आधार of the radiocarbon dating method pioneered by willard लिब्बी and सहयोगियों ( 1949 ) to date पुरातत्व, geological and hydrogeological नमूने.
carbon-14 was खोजा on 27 February 1940, by Martin कामेन और sam Ruben at the University of कैलिफ़ोर्निया Radiation प्रयोगशाला in बर्कली, although इसके अस्तित्व had been suggested by Franz kurie in 1934.
वहीँ are तीन naturally occurring isotopes of कार्बन on Earth : 99 % of the carbon is carbon-12, 1 % is carbon-13, and carbon-14 occurs in trace amounts, i.e., बनाना up परिचय 1 भाग per trillion ( 0.0000000001 % ) of the कार्बन in the माहौल.
The half-life of carbon-14 is 5,730±40 सालो.
Carbon-14 decays into nitrogen-14 through beta क्षय.
The primary प्राकृतिक source of carbon-14 on धरती is cosmic रे कार्रवाई upon nitrogen in the माहौल, and it is इसलिए a cosmogenic nuclide.
however, open-air नाभिकीय परीक्षण between 1955–1980 contributed to इस पूल.
The different isotopes of कार्बन do नहीं differ appreciably in their chemical गुण.
This is प्रयुक्त in chemical और biological research, in a तकनीक called कार्बन labeling : carbon-14 अणु can be used to replace nonradioactive कार्बन, in अनुक्रम to ट्रेस chemical and biochemical reactions involving carbon atoms from कोई दिए सशुल्क यौगिक.
बिजली is a highly दृश्य form of energy ट्रांसफ़र
Lightning हमलों हैं विद्युत discharges on a विशाल scale between the atmosphere और an earth-bound object.
वे mostly originate in thunderclouds and terminate on the ground, पुकारा Cloud to Ground ( cg ) lightning.
However, they may भी be initiated इससे a बहुत लम्बा grounded ऑब्जेक्ट and reach into the clouds.
Although `` a बिजली स्ट्राइक '' is commonly प्रयुक्त to describe सब बिजली, it is rather erroneous and a misnomer, as तभी about 25 % of सब बिजली events worldwide हैं cg, the विशाल bulk of बिजली events हैं intracloud ( ic ) or Cloud to बादल ( cc ), जहाँ निर्वहन only occurs high in the माहौल.
The वैज्ञानिक name लिये the complete process of a सिंगल lightning इवेंट is a and it is a very complex, अनेक stepped बातचीत, जिससे is नहीं completely समझा.
सबसे cg flashes तभी `` strike '' one शारीरिक location, referred to as a termination.
The प्राथमिक conducting चैनल, the उज्जवल coursing लाइट तुम may देखिए और कॉल a `` स्ट्राइक '', is तभी परिचय 1 inch in व्यास, हालांकि to our आँखें it looks much larger.
वे are मील long, upwards of tens of miles.

Thunder is सदा produced by बिजली.
Just जैसे lightning, that deceives हमारी आँखें, usually looking larger or करीब than it वाकई is, the धरती 's atmosphere and our दिमाग 's बोध of the बाहर संसार, ultimately determines whether it is `` सुना '' or not.
Lightning can नहीं happen in a वैक्यूम विहीन of ions, nor can thunder occur बगैर अणुओं to vibrate.
थंडर is a physical absolute लिये प्रत्येक सिंगल flash of बिजली.
contrary to लोकप्रिय विश्वास, a lightning strike itself is प्रायः नहीं responsible लिये अनेक मौतों or चोटों इससे a सिंगल event.
it would be impossible given the प्राकृतिक tendencies of a फ्लैश, unless लोगों or पशु यहूद stacked on top of each other, or वे यहूद somehow arranged खड़ा and part of the फ्लैश channel.
When बिजली ignites an उपलब्धियाँ ईंधन सोर्स and an विस्फोट occurs, it is the शॉक वेव or आग causing the injuries, नहीं the strike itself.
मैदान Currents, also पुकारा step potential, of an earth termination is what truly causes सबसे injuries or death to इंसानो और पशु.
the निकट instantaneous rush of surface charges, induced by the ओवरहेड thundercloud itself, race to the strike पाइंट इससे सैंकड़ों to thousands of feet दूर दौरान निर्वहन.

इस is why it is बेहतरीन to crouch, साथ फीट close together, if ever caught in the खोलें during a अंधड़.

The लड़ो रै come to represent a समय in American इतिहास जब the frontier was खोलें दायरा for outlaws opposed by law प्रवर्तन कि was स्प्रेड thin over विशाल territories, leaving some क्षेत्रों unprotected.

hdmi ( High-Definition मल्टीमीडिया Interface ) is a compact audio/video interface लिये transferring uncompressed video आंकड़ा and compressed/uncompressed डिजिटल ऑडियो data from a hdmi-compliant यंत्र ( `` the source device '' ) to a संगत computer monitor, video प्रोजेक्टर, डिजिटल टेलीविज़न, or डिजिटल ऑडियो device.
HDMI is a डिजिटल बदलना लिये मौजूदा analog वीडियो मानकों.
There हैं a क्रमांक of hdmi-standard केबल कनेक्टर्स available, each of which can be used लिये कोई uncompressed tv or PC video स्वरूप, सहित मानक, उन्नत, ऊँची definition, और 3d वीडियो सिग्नल ; up to 8 channels of संपीडित or uncompressed डिजिटल ऑडियो ; a cec ( उपभोक्ता इलेक्ट्रॉनिक्स कंट्रोल ) कनेक्शन ; और an ईथरनेट data connection.
HDMI implements the eia/cea-861 मानकों, जिससे define video स्वरुप and waveforms, हस्तांतरण of संपीडित, uncompressed, और lpcm audio, auxiliary data, और implementations of the vesa edid.
The CEC allows hdmi devices to कंट्रोल प्रत्येक अन्य जब जरुरी और allows the user to operate अनेक डिवाइस with एक रिमोट control हैंडसेट.
क्युकी hdmi is electrically compatible with the CEA-861 सिग्नल प्रयुक्त by digital विज़ुअल इंटरफ़ेस ( DVI ), no सिग्नल conversion is necessary, nor is there a घाटा of video विशेषता जब a dvi-to-hdmi एडाप्टर is प्रयुक्त.
As an uncompressed cea-861 कनेक्शन, hdmi is स्वतंत्र of the विभिन्न डिजिटल टेलीविज़न मानकों used by व्यक्तिगत डिवाइस, such as atsc and dvb, as ये हैं encapsulations of संपीडित MPEG वीडियो streams ( जिससे can be decoded and आउटपुट as an uncompressed वीडियो स्ट्रीम on hdmi ).
Production of consumer HDMI उत्पाद प्रारंभ in late 2003.
In Europe either dvi-hdcp or hdmi is शामिल in the HD ready in-store labeling specification for TV सेट लिये HDTV, formulated by eicta with ses अस्त्र in 2005.
hdmi began to appear on consumer HDTV camcorders and डिजिटल स्टिल कैमरे in 2006.
as of January 8, 2013, जिससे is टेन years बाद the release of the पहला HDMI specification, over 3 billion hdmi डिवाइस have shipped since the लॉन्च of the HDMI मानक.

Anglo-Saxon इंग्लैण्ड refers to the काल of the इतिहास of the भाग of ब्रिटेन that became ज्ञात as England, स्थायी इससे the समाप्त of Roman occupation and establishment of Anglo-Saxon kingdoms in the 5th सदी जबतक the नॉर्मन conquest of England in 1066 by विलियम the Conqueror.
anglo-saxon is a सामान्य पद referring to the Germanic peoples जो आए to Britain during the 5th and 6th सदियां, सहित Angles, saxons, Frisii, और jutes.
The term भी refers to the भाषा spoken at the समय in England, which is अभी पुकारा Old अंग्रेज़ी, and to the culture of the era, which रै long attracted लोकप्रिय और scholarly attention.
जबतक the 9th सदी Anglo-Saxon इंग्लैण्ड थी dominated by the heptarchy, the kingdoms of Northumbria, mercia, ईस्ट Anglia, एसेक्स, केंट, Sussex, और Wessex.
In शर्तें of धर्म the kingdoms followed Anglo-Saxon paganism दौरान the early काल, लकिन परिवर्तित to christianity दौरान the 7th सदी.
Paganism had a final stronghold in a period of mercian hegemony during the 640s, समाप्ति with the death of पेंदा of mercia in 655.
Facing the threat of viking invasions, the हाउस of Wessex became प्रबल दौरान the 9th सदी, अंतर्गत the नियम of Alfred the Great.
दौरान the 10th सदी, the व्यक्तिगत kingdoms unified अंतर्गत the नियम of wessex into the किंगडम of इंग्लैण्ड, which stood opposed to the danelaw, the viking kingdoms established इससे the 9th सदी in the उत्तर and east of England.
the Kingdom of इंग्लैण्ड गिरी in the Viking invasion from Denmark in 1013 and was शासित by the House of Denmark जबतक 1042, जब the anglo-saxon House of Wessex थी restored.
The last anglo-saxon king, हेरोल्ड Godwinson, थी मारे in 1066 at the बैटल of हास्टिंग्स.

View of defibrillator एलेक्ट्रोड स्थिति and placement.
defibrillation is a common treatment लिये life-threatening हृदय dysrhythmias, ventricular fibrillation, and pulseless ventricular tachycardia.
Defibrillation consists of delivering a therapeutic खुराक of विद्युत उर्जा to the affected heart साथ a यंत्र called a defibrillator.
This depolarizes a नाजुक mass of the दिल मांसपेशी, terminates the dysrhythmia, and allows सामान्य sinus लय to be reestablished by the देह 's natural pacemaker, in the sinoatrial node of the heart.
defibrillators can be external, transvenous, or implanted, depending on the type of device प्रयुक्त or needed.
Some बाह्य units, known as automated बाह्य defibrillators ( aeds ), automate the निदान of treatable लय, अर्थ कि lay responders or bystanders हैं able to use them सफलतापूर्वक साथ छोटी, or in कुछ मामले no प्रशिक्षण at all.
Gabrielle `` कोको '' bonheur Chanel ( अगस्त 19, 1883 – जनवरी 10, 1971 ) थी a फ्रेंच फ़ैशन designer and founder of the चैनल brand.
वो was the तभी fashion पंक्तियां to appear on समय पत्रिका 's सूची of the 100 सबसे influential लोगों of the 20th सदी.
साथ with Paul Poiret, चैनल was credited साथ liberating women इससे the constraints of the `` corseted silhouette '' और popularizing the acceptance of a sportive, कैज़ुअल चिक as the feminine मानक in the post- संसार युद्ध i era.
A सफल फ़ैशन creator, चैनल 's influence विस्तारित परे couture कपडे.
उसके design aesthetic थी realized in आभूषण, handbags, and महक.
Her हस्ताक्षर scent, चैनल no. 5, रै become an iconic उत्पाद.
चैनल was known for उसके lifelong determination, महत्वाकांक्षा और energy which वो लागू to उसके professional और सोशल life.
वो achieved दोनो success as a businesswoman and social prominence धन्यवाद to the कनेक्शन्स she बना through her work.
These शामिल many artists और craftspeople to जिसको वो became a संरक्षक.
however, चैनल 's अत्यधिक प्रतिस्पर्धी, opportunistic व्यक्तित्व led उसके to मेक questionable life चुनाव जिससे have उत्पन्न विवाद around her प्रतिष्ठा, विशेषकर उसके behaviour during the German occupation of फ़्रांस in संसार युद्ध ii.

रोमानिया ( ; दिनाँक spellings roumania और Rumania ; ) is a country located at the चौराहे of Central and southeastern Europe, bordering on the ब्लैक समुद्र.
रोमानिया shares a किनारा with हंगेरियाई और सर्बिया to the west, युक्त और Moldova to the पूर्वोत्तर and east, and बुल्गारिया to the south.
At, Romania is the eighth largest country of the European Union by क्षेत्रफल, and has the seventh largest population of the European Union साथ अधिक than 19 million लोगों.
इसके capital और biggest city is बुखारेस्ट, the 11th largest नगर in the eu.
The संयुक्त Principalities emerged जब the territories of moldavia और Wallachia यहूद संयुक्त under Prince सिकंदर ioan cuza in 1859.
in 1866 Prince karl of hohenzollern-sigmaringen थी called to the सिंहासन as the Ruling Prince of the रोमानियाई Principate और in 1881 he was finally पहनाया as किंग कैरोल i the पहला monarch of the Kingdom of Romania.
स्वतंत्रता इससे the उस्मानी साम्राज्य was declared on 9 may 1877, and was internationally पहचाना the following साल.
At the end of World युद्ध i, transylvania, bukovina and bessarabia संयुक्त साथ the किंगडम of रोमानिया.
संसार War ii दिया cause to the rise of a military dictatorship in Romania अंतर्गत फासिस्ट सामान्य आयन Antonescu, जो chose to लड़ो on the पक्ष of the अक्ष शक्तियां from 1941 to 1944.
After उसके हटाना, रोमानिया switched पहलू in 1944 और joined the allies.
by the end of the युद्ध, कुछ formerly रोमानियाई northeastern territories were occupied by the सोवियत संघ, साथ रेड Army units stationed on Romanian मृदा.
in 1947 रोमानिया forcibly became a लोगों 's Republic ( 1947-1965 ) and a सदस्य of the वॉरसॉ अनुबंध.
In 1965 Nicolae Ceauşescu became General सचिव of the Romanian कम्युनिस्ट Party, और the हर्ष austerity उपायों, राजनैतिक repression, और cult of personality he implemented led to the समाजवादी Republic of रोमानिया ( 1965-1989 ) बनने the most stalinist पुलिस state in the Eastern bloc.
आखिरकार उसके सत्तावादी government थी toppled in दिसम्बर 1989 दौरान the Romanian क्रान्ति of 1989.
साथ the पतन of the Iron पर्दा, रोमानिया began इसके transition towards democracy और a पूंजीवादी मार्केट economy.
After a decade of post-revolution economic problems और living-standards decline, extensive reforms fostered economic रिकवरी.
as of 2010, Romania is an upper-middle-income देश साथ a high इंसान development अनुक्रमणिका.
रोमानिया joined नाटो on 29 March 2004, और the यूरोपीय Union on 1 January 2007.
it is भी a member of the : लैटिन संघ, Francophonie, osce, WTO, BSEC, संयुक्त राष्ट्र, इत्यादि.
आज, रोमानिया is a unitary semi-presidential गणतंत्र, in जिससे the executive branch consists of the अध्यक्ष और the सरकारी.

Ancient इतिहास is the पढ़ाई of the लिखा past इससे the शुरूआत of recorded human history to the जल्दी मध्य Ages.
the स्पैन of अंकित इतिहास is roughly 5,000 years, with Cuneiform स्क्रिप्ट, the oldest discovered रूप of सुसंगत लिखने, इससे the protoliterate काल around the 30th century BC.
इस is the शुरूआत of इतिहास, as opposed to प्रागितिहास, according to the परिभाषा प्रयुक्त by most historians.
the पद शास्त्रीय प्राचीनता is often प्रयुक्त to refer to इतिहास in the बूढ़ा संसार from the शुरूआत of अंकित यूनानी इतिहास in 776 bc ( पहला Olympiad ).
This roughly coincides with the परंपरागत तिथि of the founding of Rome in 753 BC, the शुरूआत of the history of प्राचीन रोम, and the शुरूआत of the archaic काल in प्राचीन यूनानियों.
हालांकि the ending date of प्राचीन history is विवादित, some पश्चिमी scholars उपयोग the पतन of the Western Roman साम्राज्य in 476 AD, the closure of the platonic Academy in 529 AD, the मौत of the सम्राट Justinian i, the coming of islam or the वृद्धि of शारलेमेन as the समाप्त of प्राचीन and Classical European इतिहास.
in इण्डिया, the काल शामिल the early काल of the Middle kingdoms, और, in China, the समय up to the qin राजवंश is शामिल.
Methylcobalamin ( दिखाया ) is a form of vitamin B12.
physically it resembles the अन्य forms of विटामिन b12, occurring as अंधेरा रेड crystals कि freely form cherry-colored transparent समाधान in जल.
विटामिन b12, vitamin B12 or विटामिन B-12, also called cobalamin, is a water-soluble विटामिन साथ a कुंजी role in the normal functioning of the brain and बेचैन प्रणाली, और लिये the formation of रक्त.
it is one of the आठ B विटामिन.
It is सामान्यतः शामिल in the चयापचय of every cell of the human body, विशेषकर affecting DNA synthesis and विनियमन, लकिन भी fatty acid संश्लेषण और energy उत्पादन.
neither fungi, plants, nor animals हैं सक्षम of producing vitamin B12.
तभी जीवाणु और archaea have the enzymes जरूरी लिये इसके संश्लेषण, although many भोजन हैं a natural सोर्स of B12 क्युकी of बैक्टीरियल symbiosis.
the vitamin is the largest and most structurally complicated vitamin and can be उत्पादित industrially only through bacterial fermentation-synthesis.
विटामिन B12 consists of a class of chemically सम्बन्धित यौगिकों ( vitamers ), सब of जिससे have vitamin कार्यकलाप.
It contains the biochemically rare तत्व cobalt.
Biosynthesis of the मौलिक structure of the विटामिन is संपन्नता तभी by जीवाणु ( जिससे प्रायः उपज hydroxocobalamin ), लकिन conversion between different फ़ॉर्म of the vitamin can be accomplished in the इंसान body.
a आम semi-synthetic रूप of the विटामिन, cyanocobalamin, करता नहीं occur in nature, but is produced इससे bacterial hydroxocobalamin और तब used in अनेक दवाएँ और पूरक, और as a food योगात्मक, क्युकी of इसके स्थिरता and lower उत्पादन लागत.
In the देह it is converted to the इंसान physiological forms methylcobalamin और adenosylcobalamin, leaving behind the साइनाइड, albeit in minimal विशेषज्ञता.
अधिक recently, hydroxocobalamin, methylcobalamin, and adenosylcobalamin can be found in अधिक expensive pharmacological उत्पाद and खाना पूरक.
the अतिरिक्त यूटिलिटी of ये is फिलहाल debated.
Vitamin b12 थी discovered from इसके relationship to the बीमारी घातक anemia, जिससे is an असंक्राम्य बीमारी in जिससे parietal कोशिकाएं of the stomach responsible लिये secreting मूलभूत factor हैं destroyed.
Intrinsic factor is निर्णायक लिये the सामान्य अवशोषण of B12, so a कमी of मूलभूत फ़ैक्टर, as seen in pernicious anemia, causes a विटामिन b12 कमियां.
Many अन्य subtler kinds of vitamin b12 कमियां और उनके biochemical effects have since महरूम elucidated.
the रोमन Empire ( ) थी the post- रिपब्लिकन period of the प्राचीन रोमन सभ्यता, characterised by an autocratic रूप of सरकारी और विशाल territorial holdings around the Mediterranean in Europe, Africa, और Asia.
the 500-year-old रोमन गणतंत्र, which preceded it, था महरूम destabilized through a series of सिविल wars.
अनेक events चिह्नित the परिवर्तन इससे गणतंत्र to Empire, including Julius सीज़र 's नियुक्ति as perpetual तानाशाह ( 44 BC ) ; the Battle of Actium ( 31 BC ) ; और the granting of the honorific augustus to Octavian by the रोमन Senate ( 27 BC ).
The पहला two सदियां of the साम्राज्य यहूद a काल of unprecedented stability और समृद्धि ज्ञात as the pax romana ( `` रोमन सलाम '' ).
It पहुँचे its महानतम expanse दौरान the reign of त्राजान ( 98–117 ad ).
in the 3rd सदी, the Empire underwent a crisis कि threatened इसके existence, but थी reunified and stabilized under the emperors Aurelian and diocletian.
Christians रोज़ to power in the 4th century, दौरान जिससे time a प्रणाली of dual rule was विकसित in the लैटिन वेस्ट and यूनानी East.
बाद the पतन of सेंट्रल government in the वेस्ट in the 5th century, the eastern हाफ जारी as कया होता later be ज्ञात as the बीज़ान्टिन साम्राज्य.
Because of the साम्राज्य 's vast extent and long सहनशीलता, the संस्थानों और संस्कृति of Rome had a profound और स्थायी influence on the development of language, धर्म, architecture, दर्शनशास्त्र, विधि, and फ़ॉर्म of government in the territory it governed, विशेषकर यूरोपीय, and by अर्थात् of European expansionism throughout the आधुनिक संसार.

the degree symbol ( ° ) is a typographical प्रतीक that is प्रयुक्त, among other things, to represent डिग्री of चाप ( e.g. in geographic निर्देशांक प्रणालियों ), घंटों ( in the चिकित्सा फ़ील्ड ), or डिग्री of temperature.
the symbol consists of a small उठाया वृत्त, historically a शून्य glyph.

This is a सूची of जड़ें, प्रत्यय, और prefixes प्रयुक्त in चिकित्सा शब्दावली, उनके meanings, and उनके etymology.
There हैं a few rules जब using चिकित्सा जड़ें.
firstly, prefixes और प्रत्यय, primarily in Greek, लकिन also in Latin, have a droppable -o-.
as a सामान्य नियम, इस -o- लगभग सदा अधिनियमों as a joint-stem to connect दो consonantal जड़ें, e.g. arthr- + -o- + logy = arthrology.
But generally, the -o- is dropped when connecting to a vowel-stem ; e.g. arthr- + itis = गठिया, बजाय of arthr-o-itis.
secondly, चिकित्सा जड़ें generally go साथ according to भाषा : यूनानी prefixes go साथ यूनानी प्रत्यय and लैटिन prefixes with Latin suffixes.
Although अंतरराष्ट्रीय scientific शब्दावली is not stringent परिचय segregating combining फ़ॉर्म of different भाषाएं, it is advisable जब coining नई शब्द not to mix अलग lingual जड़ें.
पेट कर्कट, or gastric cancer, refers to कर्कट arising from कोई भाग of the stomach.

The संसार 's प्रिंसिपल religions और आध्यात्मिक परंपराओं may be classified into a छोटी number of प्रमुख समूह, हालांकि this is by no means a uniform अभ्यास.
इस सिद्धान्त began in the 18th century with the goal of recognizing the सापेक्ष स्तर of civility in societies.

The बर्लिन blockade ( 24 June 1948 – 12 may 1949 ) थी एक of the first major अंतरराष्ट्रीय crises of the ठंडा War.
दौरान the multinational occupation of post–World War ii जर्मनी, the सोवियत संघ blocked the पश्चिमी Allies ' रेल, सड़क, and canal अभिगम to the sectors of Berlin under Allied control.
उनके aim was to फ़ोर्स the western शक्तियां to allow the सोवियत मण्डल to प्रारंभ supplying बर्लिन साथ food और fuel, thereby giving the soviets practical कंट्रोल over the entire नगर.
In response, the पश्चिमी allies organized the Berlin एयरलिफ्ट to carry आपूर्तियाँ to the लोगों in वेस्ट बर्लिन.
aircrews from the United राज्य एयर फ़ोर्स, the British Royal Air फ़ोर्स, the Royal Australian एयर Force, the Royal कनाडाई एयर फ़ोर्स, the Royal New जीलैंड Air Force, and the दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी Air फ़ोर्स flew over 200,000 फ़्लाइट in एक साल, providing up to 4700 tons of रोज़ necessities such as fuel और खाना to the berliners.
By the वसन्त of 1949, the प्रयत्न थी clearly succeeding and, by अप्रैल, the airlift थी delivering अधिक cargo than था previously been transported into the नगर by रेल.
The कामयाबी of the बर्लिन एयरलिफ्ट brought embarrassment to the soviets जो था refused to मानना it could make a अंतर.
The नाकेबंदी थी lifted in may 1949 और resulted in the सृष्टि of two separate German राज्य.
the संघीय Republic of जर्मनी ( वेस्ट जर्मनी ) और the German Democratic Republic ( East Germany ) विभाजित up बर्लिन.
In स्मरण of the एयरलिफ्ट, तीन एयरपोर्ट in the former western zones of the नगर परोसा as the प्राथमिक gateways to जर्मनी लिये another पचास सालो.

the डिज़ाइन थी प्रस्तुत to the public by the यूरोपीय आयोग on 12 दिसम्बर 1996.

In युनिकोड it is encoded at.

in कुछ styleguides, लकिन नहीं अन्य, the euro चिह्न is unspaced.
mate (, ; sometimes भी spelled maté ), भी ज्ञात as chimarrão ( ) or cimarrón ( ), is a परंपरागत दक्षिण American infused drink, विशेषकर in Argentina, उरुग्वे, पैराग्वे and the southern states of Brazil और to a lesser उपाधि in दक्षिण of चिली, the bolivian Chaco, Syria और Lebanon.
It is prepared from steeping dried leaves of yerba mate ( llex paraguariensis, ज्ञात in Portuguese as erva-mate ) in hot जल.
mate is परोसा with a मेटल स्ट्रॉ इससे a साझा hollow calabash करेले.
the straw is called a bombilla in some लैटिन American countries, a bomba in पुर्तगाली, और a bombija or, more generally, a masassa ( प्रकार of स्ट्रॉ ) in अरबी.
The straw is traditionally made of चांदी.
Modern, commercially उपलब्धियाँ straws हैं typically बना of निकल चांदी, पुकारा Alpaca ; बेदाग स्टील, or hollow-stemmed cane.
The करेले is known as a mate or a guampa ; while in Brazil, it has the विशिष्ट नाम of cuia, or भी cabaça ( the नाम लिये indigenous-influenced calabash gourds in अन्य regions of ब्राज़ील, still प्रयुक्त लिये general food और पेय in रिमोट regions ).
Even if the जल is supplied from a modern thermos, the infusion is traditionally नशे इससे mates or cuias.
As साथ other brewed herbs, yerba mate पत्ते are सूखी, chopped, and मैदान into a powdery मिश्रण called yerba.
the bombilla अधिनियमों as दोनो a straw और a sieve.
The submerged end is flared, with small holes or slots कि allow the brewed द्रव in, but ब्लाक the चंकी पदार्थ that makes up much of the मिश्रण.
a आधुनिक bombilla डिज़ाइन uses a straight tube with छेद, or वसन्त sleeve to act as a sieve.
`` Tea-bag '' प्रकार infusions of mate ( mate cocido ) have महरूम on the market in अर्जेंटीना, Paraguay and उरुग्वे लिये अनेक सालो अंतर्गत ऐसे व्यापार names as `` taragüí vitality '' in अर्जेंटीना, `` pajarito '' और `` kurupí '' in पैराग्वे, and in Brazil under the नाम `` Mate Leão ''.
इस is माना a completely अलग drink.
It is never drunk इससे cuias or पुकारा chimarrão, nor is it associated साथ the gaucho/gaúcho संस्कृति.
the ऑटोमोटिव उद्योग is a term कि कवर a चौड़ी दायरा of कंपनियाँ और संगठनों involved in the design, development, manufacture, विपणन, और selling of motor वाहनों, towed वाहनों, मोटरसाइकिल and mopeds.
it is एक of the world 's सबसे महत्वपूर्ण आर्थिक सेक्टर by आय.
The पद ऑटोमोटिव उद्योग usually करता not शामिल industries समर्पित to the maintenance of automobiles following delivery to the end-user, ऐसे as मरम्मत दुकानें और मोटर fuel भरना स्टेशन.
the term ऑटोमोटिव was निर्मित from यूनानी autos ( स्वः ), और लैटिन motivus ( of गति ) to represent any रूप of self-powered गाडी.
इस पद थी proposed by SAE सदस्य एल्मर स्पेरी.

हैलोवीन or hallowe'en ( a contraction of `` सब Hallows ' संध्या `` ), भी known as सब Hallows ' संध्या, is a वार्षिक जश्न observed in a number of देशों on अक्तूबर 31, the eve of the Western ईसाई feast of All Hallows ( or सब संतो ) and the दिन initiating the triduum of hallowmas.
according to अनेक विद्वानों, All Hallows ' संध्या is a christianised feast originally बहकावे by पश्चिमी यूरोपीय कटाई त्यौहार, और festivals of the dead with संभावित pagan जड़ें, विशेषकर the Celtic Samhain.
अन्य scholars maintain that it originated independently of samhain and has solely ईसाई roots.
ठेठ त्यौहार हैलोवीन activities include trick-or-treating ( भी ज्ञात as `` guising `` ), उपस्थित वेशभूषा parties, नक्काशी pumpkins into jack-o'-lanterns, lighting bonfires, apple bobbing, visiting haunted attractions, playing pranks, telling scary कहानियां, and watching हॉरर films.
स्वतंत्रता of speech is the political सही to communicate one 's राय and ideas using one 's देह and property to anyone who is willing to receive उन्हें.
The term freedom of अभिव्यक्ति is sometimes प्रयुक्त synonymously, लकिन शामिल कोई अधिनियम of seeking, receiving and imparting information or ideas, regardless of the मीडियम used.
in अभ्यास, the right to freedom of वाक is नहीं निरपेक्ष in कोई देश and the सही is commonly विषय to सीमाएं, as साथ libel, बदनामी, obscenity, राजद्रोह ( including, for उदाहरण inciting जातीय hatred ), कापीराइट violation, रहस्योद्घाटन of सूचना that is classified or otherwise.
The सही to स्वतंत्रता of expression is पहचाना as a human right अंतर्गत आलेख 19 of the Universal घोषणा of Human Rights और पहचाना in अंतरराष्ट्रीय human अधिकारों विधि in the International Covenant on Civil और राजनैतिक अधिकारों ( ICCPR ).
Article 19 of the ICCPR states कि `` [ e ] veryone shall have the right to थाम opinions बगैर हस्तक्षेप '' and `` everyone shall have the सही to freedom of अभिव्यक्ति ; this सही shall शामिल freedom to तलाश, receive और impart information और विचार of all kinds, regardless of frontiers, either orally, in लिखने or in print, in the रूप of art, or through कोई अन्य मीडिया of उसके चुनाव ''.
आलेख 19 goes on to say that the exercise of ये अधिकारों carries `` खास duties and responsibilities `` और may `` therefore be subject to निश्चित प्रतिबंध '' जब necessary `` [ f ] or respect of the rights or reputation of others '' or `` [ f ] or the protection of नेशनल सुरक्षा or of public order ( order public ), or of public स्वास्थ्य or नैतिकता ''.
Freedom of speech may be legally curtailed in कुछ धार्मिक legal प्रणालियों और in secular jurisdictions where it is मिला to कारण धार्मिक ठोकर, ऐसे as the British जातिगत और धार्मिक द्वेष Act 2006.
सिडनी harbour इससे the एयर, प्रर्दशित the Opera House, the सीबीडी, Circular quay, the सेतु, the Parramatta नदी, उत्तर Sydney and Kirribilli in the अग्रभूमि
the Sydney Harbour सेतु is a steel through arch bridge आरपार सिडनी harbour that carries रेल, vehicular, सायकिल and पैदल traffic between the सिडनी सेंट्रल कारोबार district ( सीबीडी ) और the North Shore.
the नाटकीय view of the सेतु, the harbour, और the आसपास सिडनी ओपेरा हाउस is an iconic चित्र of सिडनी, New South Wales, and ऑस्ट्रेलिया.
the bridge is nicknamed `` the Coathanger '' because of its arch-based डिज़ाइन.
Under the दिशानिर्देश of dr j.j.c. bradfield of the nsw विभाग of Public Works, the सेतु थी designed और निर्मित by अंग्रेजों firm dorman long and co Ltd of Middlesbrough और opened in 1932.
the bridge 's डिज़ाइन थी influenced by the Hell फाटक सेतु in नई यॉर्क.
it थी the संसार 's widest long-span सेतु, at 48.8 मीटर ( 160 फीट ) wide, until निर्माण of the new Port Mann सेतु in Vancouver.
it is also the fifth longest spanning-arch सेतु in the संसार, and it is the tallest स्टील मेहराब bridge, measuring इससे शीर्ष to जल स्तर.
जबतक 1967 the Harbour सेतु was सिडनी 's tallest ढांचा.
the हवाई हॉटस्पॉट is a volcanic हॉटस्पॉट स्तिथ निकट the namesake हवाई आइलैंड्स, in the उत्तरी प्रशांत समंदर.
एक of the most well-known और heavily पढ़ाई हॉटस्पॉट in the संसार, the Hawaii plume is जिम्मेदार for the सृष्टि of the हवाई – Emperor seamount chain, an over 5,800 किलोमीटर ( 3,600 mi ) long chain of volcanoes, चार of जिससे हैं active, दो of which are dormant, और अधिक than 123 of which हैं विलुप्त, अनेक having चूंकि been ground beneath the लहरें by erosion as seamounts and atolls.
The chain extends from दक्षिण of the द्वीप of Hawaii to the किनारे of the aleutian गर्त, निकट the eastern edge of Russia.
While most ज्वालामुखी are निर्मित by geological activity at tectonic plate सीमाएँ, the हवाई हॉटस्पॉट is स्तिथ far इससे आसपास plate सीमाएँ ; the classic hotspot सिद्धान्त, पहला प्रस्तावित in 1963 by जॉन Tuzo विल्सन, proposes that a सिंगल, फिक्स्ड mantle plume builds ज्वालामुखी कि तब, cut बंद from उनके सोर्स by the गति of the प्रशांत थाली, become increasingly inactive and आखिरकार erode नीचे sea स्तर over लाखो of सालो.
according to इस सिद्धान्त, the nearly 60° bend separating the सम्राट और Hawaiian segments of the कड़ी थी caused by a sudden shift in the गति of the Pacific थाली.
In 2003, भैस investigations of this irregularity led to the proposal of a मोबाईल हॉटस्पॉट सिद्धान्त, suggesting कि हॉटस्पॉट are mobile, नहीं फिक्स्ड, and that the 47 लाख साल बूढ़ा बेंड was caused by a shift in the हॉटस्पॉट 's motion बल्कि than the थाली 's.
प्राचीन hawaiians were the first to recognize the increasing आयु and weathered राज्य of the volcanoes to the north as they progressed on fishing रिझाने साथ the islands.
the volatile state of the हवाई ज्वालामुखी और their निरंतर battle साथ the sea थी a major तत्व in हवाई mythology, समाविष्ट in pele, the deity of ज्वालामुखी.
बाद the arrival of europeans on the island, in 1880-1881 जेम्स Dwight दाना directed the पहला formal geological study of the hotspot 's volcanics, confirming the संबंध long observed by the natives.
1912 चिह्नित the founding of the Hawaiian Volcano Observatory by volcanologist Thomas jaggar, initiating निरन्तर वैज्ञानिक observation of the आइलैंड्स.
In the 1970s, a mapping प्रोजेक्ट was initiated to लाभ अधिक सूचना परिचय the complex geology of हवाई 's seafloor.
The हॉटस्पॉट रै चूंकि महरूम tomographically imaged, प्रर्दशित it to be चौड़ी और up to deep, और ओलीवाइन और गार्नेट -आधारd अध्ययन have shown its मैग्मा कक्ष is लगभग.
In its at least 85 million years of activity the हॉटस्पॉट रै produced an estimated of rock.
the कड़ी 's rate of बहाव रै slowly increased over time, causing the राशि of time प्रत्येक व्यक्तिगत volcano is active to घटी, इससे 18 million सालो लिये the 76 million साल old Detroit seamount, to बस under 900,000 for the एक लाख year-old Kohala ; on the अन्य हाथ, eruptive आवाज़ has increased इससे प्रति साल to परिचय.
overall, इस रै caused a ट्रेंड towards अधिक active but quickly-silenced, closely spaced volcanoes—whereas ज्वालामुखी on the निकट पक्ष of the हॉटस्पॉट ओवरलैप प्रत्येक अन्य ( forming ऐसे superstructures as Hawaii द्वीप और the ancient मावी नुई ), the oldest of the सम्राट seamounts are spaced as far as अलावा.

osteonecrosis of the jaw ( onj ) is a severe bone बीमारी that affects the maxilla and the mandible.
Various forms of ONJ have महरूम described over the पिछला 160 सालो, and a क्रमांक of कल्याणकारी have been सुझाया in the साहित्य.
osteonecrosis of the जबड़े associated साथ bisphosphonate therapy, जरूरी by कुछ कर्कट उपचार regimens, रै been identified और पारिभाषित as a pathological एंटिटी चूंकि 2003.
The संभावित रिस्क from निम्नतर oral doses of bisphosphonates, लिया by मरीजों to prevent or दावत ऑस्टियोपोरोसिस, remains uncertain.

mince पाई filled with mincemeat
Mincemeat is a मिश्रण of कटा dried फल, आसुत spirits और spices, और sometimes beef suet, बीफ, or venison.
Originally, mincemeat always contained meat.
अनेक आधुनिक व्यंजनों contain बीफ suet, हालांकि vegetable shortening is sometimes used in इसके place.

in कुछ countries the पद mincemeat refers to minced or मैदान मांस.

अर्जेंटीना, officially the Argentine गणतंत्र ( ), is the second largest देश in दोनो दक्षिण अमेरिका और the लैटिन अमेरिका region.
The देश is a संघ of 23 provinces और the autonomous नगर of buenos Aires, इसके capital और largest नगर.
it is the आठवीं -largest देश in the world by land area और the largest among spanish-speaking राष्ट्र by भौगोलिक area of 2,780,400 km2 and is the fourth by जनसांख्यिकी, with over 41 लाख people.
अर्जेंटीना is a founding member of the United राष्ट्र, mercosur, the संघ of दक्षिण अमरीकी Nations, the Organization of Ibero-American राज्य, the World बैंको समूह and the संसार व्यापार संगठन, और is one of the g-15 और G-20 major economies.
अर्जेंटीना is located in South America, bordered by चिली to the वेस्ट और south, Bolivia और पैराग्वे to the north और ब्राज़ील and उरुग्वे to the northeast.
अर्जेंटीना claims प्रभुता over part of अंटार्कटिक, the फ़ॉकलैंड आइलैंड्स ( ) और South Georgia और the दक्षिण Sandwich Islands.
Argentina is the successor राज्य of the Viceroyalty of the río de la प्लाटा, an विदेशी उपनिवेश of the स्पेनी Empire.
Argentina घोषित स्वतंत्रता दौरान the अर्जेंटाइन War of स्वतंत्रता, जिससे was followed by the अर्जेंटाइन सिविल युद्धों during सबसे of the 19th सदी.
the देश faced several सैन्य coups and राजनैतिक instability during the 20th century, साथ with आवधिक आर्थिक संकट that continue to this day.
A पहचाना Southern कोन power, और मध्य power, Argentina is लैटिन America 's third-largest अर्थव्यवस्था, with a `` बहुत high '' rating on the इंसान विकास index.
भीतर Latin अमेरिका, अर्जेंटीना has the fifth उच्चतम nominal जीडीपी प्रति capita और the highest in खरीदना power शर्तें.
the legatum संस्थान have argued कि the देश has a `` न्यास for भविष्य विकास due to इसके market size, levels of विदेशी सीधा investment, और प्रतिशत of high-tech निर्यात as share of कुल manufactured goods '', and it is classed by investors as मध्य emerging अर्थव्यवस्था.
अर्जेंटीना is the लैटिन अमरीकी country with the सबसे नोबेल पुरस्कार, for a कुल of पाँच, सब प्राप्त दौरान the दूसरी हाफ of the बीसवीं सदी.
the country has तीन Nobel पुरस्कार in विज्ञान और two of peace.
The सबसे महत्वपूर्ण aspects of विज्ञान और प्रौद्योगिकी in अर्जेंटीना are चिंतित with medicine, नाभिकीय भौतिकी, जैवप्रौद्योगिकी, nanotechnology, स्पेस और प्रक्षेपास्त्र प्रौद्योगिकी and अनेक फ़ील्ड related to the देश 's प्रमुख आर्थिक क्रियाएँ.
the country भी has the mega प्रदर्शनी center of विज्ञान, प्रौद्योगिकी, उद्योग और art that हैं लैटिन अमेरिका 's largest.

polyethylene terephthalate ( sometimes written poly ( ethylene terephthalate ) ), commonly abbreviated पालतु, पीट, or the obsolete petp or pet-p, is a thermoplastic पॉलिमर राल of the पॉलिएस्टर परिवार और is प्रयुक्त in सिंथेटिक मछली ; पेय, खाना और अन्य द्रव containers ; thermoforming applications ; and engineering resins often in combination साथ कांच रेशा.
the term polyethylene terephthalate is a सोर्स of confusion क्युकी this substance, PET, does नहीं contain polyethylene.
Thus, the वैकल्पिक form, बहु ( ethylene terephthalate ), is प्रायः प्रयुक्त in scholarly जर्नल्स लिये the sake of सटीकता और स्पष्टता.
depending on its प्रसंस्करण और thermal इतिहास, polyethylene terephthalate may मौजूद both as an amorphous ( पारदर्शी ) and as a semi-crystalline पॉलिमर.
the semicrystalline material might appear पारदर्शी ( particle size < 500 nm ) or अपारदर्शी and white ( particle आकार up to a few माइक्रोन ) depending on its क्रिस्टल ढांचा and कण आकार.
Its मोनोमर ( bis-β-hydroxyterephthalate ) can be synthesized by the esterification प्रतिक्रिया between terephthalic acid and एथिलीन glycol with जल as a byproduct, or by transesterification प्रतिक्रिया between एथिलीन ग्लाइकोल and dimethyl terephthalate साथ methanol as a byproduct.
बहुलकीकरण is through a polycondensation reaction of the monomers ( done तत्काल बाद esterification/transesterification ) साथ जल as the byproduct.
the majority of the संसार 's पालतु production is लिये सिंथेटिक मछली ( in excess of 60 % ), साथ bottle उत्पादन accounting for around 30 % of वैश्विक माँग.
in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of वस्त्र applications, पालतु is referred to by its common name, `` polyester, '' whereas the acronym `` PET '' is generally प्रयुक्त in संबंध to पैकेजिंग.
Polyester makes up about 18 % of world पॉलिमर production और is the third-most-produced polymer ; polyethylene ( pe ) and polypropylene ( pp ) are first and दूसरी, क्रमशः.
पालतु consists of polymerized units of the मोनोमर एथिलीन terephthalate, with repeating c10h8o4 units.
पालतु is commonly recycled, और रै the क्रमांक `` 1 '' as इसके रीसाइक्लिंग symbol.

ब्लैक खीर, blood pudding or रक्त सॉसेज is a प्रकार of सॉसेज बना by कुकिंग blood or सूखी रक्त with a filler जबतक it is मोटा enough to congeal when cooled.
the डिश exists in various संस्कृतियों from एशिया to Europe and the americas.
सुअर, cattle, शीप, बतख, और बकरी रक्त can be used depending on अलग देशों.
in Europe and the Americas, ठेठ fillers include meat, मोटे, suet, ब्रैड, cornmeal, sweet potato, प्याज, chestnuts, जौ, और oatmeal.
in Spain, पुर्तगाल और Asia, potato is often replaced by rice.
शेयरधारक may refer to:
शेयरधारक ( corporate ), a person, समूह, organization, सदस्य or system who affects or can be affected by an संगठन 's क्रियाएँ
Stakeholder, an entity कि can be affected by the परिणाम of कि in जिससे they are said to be stakeholders, i.e., कि in which वे have a हिस्सेदारी.
प्रोजेक्ट शेयरधारक, a व्यक्ति, समूह or संगठन साथ an interest in a project
Stakeholder theory, a theory that identifies और मॉडल the समूह जिससे are हितधारकों of a निगम or प्रोजेक्ट
शेयरधारक analysis, the process of identifying those प्रभावित by a प्रोजेक्ट or event
शेयरधारक ( विधि ), a third party जो temporarily holds धन or property while its owner is स्टिल होने determined

उसके film credits include The Traveling Executioner, Rabbit, चलाएं, Loving युगल, मिडवे, हार्पर, Airport 1975, Damnation Alley और the Emmy पुरस्कार -winning एडी, as खूब as many episodes of टेलीविज़न series ऐसे as the Twilight मण्डल और The Alfred हिचकॉक घंटा.

साथ a population of approximately 201,165 at the 2010 census, modesto ranks as the 18th largest नगर in the state of California.
The Modesto जनसांख्यिकी काउंटी प्रभाग, which शामिल the शहरों of ceres और Riverbank, रै a जनसांख्यिकी of 312,842 as of 2010.

स्वतंत्रता दिन, commonly ज्ञात as the Fourth of जुलाई, is a federal अवकाश in the संयुक्त States commemorating the अपनाना of the Declaration of स्वतंत्रता on जुलाई 4, 1776, declaring स्वतंत्रता इससे the किंगडम of ग्रेट ब्रिटेन.
स्वतंत्रता Day is commonly संबद्ध with आतिशबाजी, parades, barbecues, carnivals, fairs, picnics, concerts, बेसबॉल games, परिवार reunions, and political speeches and ceremonies, in जोड to विभिन्न other पब्लिक और private कार्यक्रम celebrating the इतिहास, सरकारी, और traditions of the संयुक्त राज्य.

a gender symbol denotes the sex of an सजीव or characterizes an एजेंट by लिंग.
The दो मानक लिंग symbols denoting male ♂ and female ♀ are निकला इससे astrological symbols, denoting the शास्त्रीय planets मंगल और शुक्र, respectively.

a leasehold estate is an स्वामित्व of a अस्थाई सही to थाम जमीन or प्रॉपर्टी in which a lessee or a tenant holds अधिकारों of रियल प्रॉपर्टी by कुछ रूप of शीर्षक इससे a lessor or landlord.
हालांकि a किरायेदार does थाम अधिकारों to रियल प्रॉपर्टी, a leasehold estate is typically माना personal प्रॉपर्टी.
Leasehold is a form of जमीन कार्यकाल or प्रॉपर्टी कार्यकाल जहाँ एक पार्टी खरीदता the right to occupy जमीन or a भवन for a दिए लंबाई of time.
as पट्टे is a विधिक एस्टेट, leasehold एस्टेट can be खरीदा and sold on the open मार्केट.
a leasehold thus differs इससे a freehold or शुल्क simple जहाँ the ownership of a प्रॉपर्टी is purchased outright and thereafter held for an indeterminate length of समय, और भी differs इससे a tenancy जहाँ a प्रॉपर्टी is let ( rented ) on a periodic आधार ऐसे as weekly or मासिक.
जबतक the समाप्त of the पट्टे काल ( प्रायः measured in दशकों or centuries ; a 99 year lease is काफी आम ) the leaseholder रै the सही to remain in occupation as an assured किरायेदार paying an सहमत rent to the owner.
Terms of the अनुबंध are contained in a पट्टे, जिससे has तत्व of अनुबंध और प्रॉपर्टी विधि intertwined.
the term estate लिये years may occasionally be used.
इस refers to a leasehold estate लिये कोई specific काल of time ( the शब्द `` years '' is भ्रामक ).
An एस्टेट for सालो is नहीं automatically नवीनीकृत.
Colloquially, `` lease '' और `` पट्टे `` हैं प्रायः a formalization of a longer, specific काल as compared with a `` rental '' कि निर्मित a tenancy at will, terminable or बेदर्दी at the समाप्त of a short काल.

The पनामा कनाल ( ) is a जलयान canal in पनामा कि connects the अटलांटिक समंदर ( via the Caribbean समुद्र ) to the प्रशांत समंदर.
The कनाल कटौती across the Isthmus of Panama and is a key conduit लिये अंतरराष्ट्रीय मेरीटाइम व्यापार.
There हैं locks at प्रत्येक समाप्त to लिफ्ट जहाजों up to Gatun Lake ( above sea-level ).
gatun झील थी निर्मित to reduce the amount of कार्य जरूरी लिये the कनाल.
the वर्तमान ताले हैं चौड़ी.
a third, wider lane of locks is होने built.
फ़्रांस began work on the canal in 1881, लकिन था to रोकें because of अभियान्त्रिकी समस्याएं and high mortality due to बीमारी.
the संयुक्त राज्य ( US ) later took over the प्रोजेक्ट और took a दशक to complete the canal in 1914, enabling ships to avoid the lengthy Cape सींग route around the southernmost tip of दक्षिण अमेरिका ( via the ड्रेक Passage ) or to navigate the Strait of magellan.
एक of the largest and सबसे मुश्किल engineering प्रोजेक्ट कभी undertaken, the पनामा कनाल शॉर्टकट बना it possible लिये जहाजों to सफर between the अटलांटिक और Pacific महासागर in half the time previously required.
the shorter, faster, safer route to the us वेस्ट coast और to राष्ट्र in और साथ the Pacific Ocean अनुमत those places to become more एकीकृत with the संसार अर्थव्यवस्था.
दौरान इस समय, ownership of the territory कि is now the पनामा Canal थी पहला Colombian, तब French, और तब American ; the संयुक्त राज्य समाप्त the निर्माण.
The कनाल थी taken over in 1999 by the Panamanian सरकारी, as long नियोजित.
सालाना traffic has risen इससे परिचय 1,000 ships जब the canal खोली in 1914, to 14,702 vessels in 2008, the latter measuring a total of 309.6 million Panama Canal/Universal Measurement System ( pc/ums ) टन.
By 2008, अधिक than 815,000 vessels था passed through the canal, many of them much larger than the असली planners could have envisioned ; the largest ships that can पारगमन the canal today हैं पुकारा panamax.
The American Society of Civil Engineers रै named the पनामा Canal एक of the सात चमत्कार of the आधुनिक world.
बेंजामिन फ्रैंकलिन ( अप्रैल 17, 1790 ) थी one of the founding fathers of the United States.
a noted बहुश्रुत, Franklin was a leading लेखक, मुद्रक, राजनैतिक theorist, politician, postmaster, scientist, musician, inventor, satirist, नागरिक activist, statesman, और राजनयिक.
as a वैज्ञानिक, he थी a प्रमुख figure in the अमरीकी आत्मज्ञान and the history of भौतिकी for उसके discoveries और theories regarding विद्युत.
he invented the lightning rod, bifocals, the फ्रैंकलिन स्टोव, a carriage odometer, और the कांच 'armonica '.
He facilitated अनेक civic संगठन, including a आग विभाग और a university.
Franklin earned the title of `` The First अमरीकी '' for उसके जल्दी और indefatigable campaigning लिये औपनिवेशिक unity ; as an लेखक and spokesman in लंदन for several colonies, तब as the first United States दूत to फ़्रांस, he सरंचनाओं the emerging अमरीकी स्वदेश.
फ्रैंकलिन was foundational in धमक the अमरीकी ethos as a विवाह of the व्यावहारिक मान of thrift, hard कार्य, education, community spirit, self-governing संस्थानों, and विपक्ष to authoritarianism दोनो राजनैतिक and धार्मिक, साथ the वैज्ञानिक and सहिष्णु मान of the Enlightenment.
In the words of इतिहासकार हेनरी स्टील commager, `` In a Franklin could be मिलाया the virtues of puritanism बगैर इसके defects, the illumination of the आत्मज्ञान बगैर इसके heat. ''
to Walter isaacson, this makes फ्रैंकलिन `` the सबसे accomplished अमरीकी of उसके age और the सबसे influential in inventing the प्रकार of समाज America होता become. ''
Franklin, सदा proud of his working क्लास जड़ें, became a कामयाब newspaper editor और मुद्रक in Philadelphia, the leading city in the colonies.
He was also partners साथ विलियम Goddard और जोसेफ गैलोवे the तीन of whom published the पेन्सिलवेनिया Chronicle, a newspaper कि was ज्ञात for इसके revolutionary sentiments और आलोचनाओं of the अंग्रेजों साम्राज्य in the अमरीकी colonies.
He became धनवान प्रकाशन ग़रीब Richard 's Almanack and the पेन्सिलवेनिया गजट.
फ्रैंकलिन gained international renown as a वैज्ञानिक लिये his प्रसिद्ध प्रयोग in electricity और लिये उसके अनेक आविष्कारों, especially the बिजली लाठी.
he played a major भूमिका in establishing the University of पेन्सिलवेनिया और was elected the पहला अध्यक्ष of the American philosophical समाज.
Franklin became a national hero in अमेरिका when he पथप्रदर्शन the effort to have Parliament repeal the unpopular स्टैम्प अधिनियम.
An संपन्नता राजनयिक, he was widely admired among the French as अमरीकी मंत्री to Paris और was a major फिगर in the development of धनात्मक franco-american संबंध.
लिये अनेक सालो he थी the अंग्रेजों postmaster लिये the colonies, which enabled him to नियत up the पहला नेशनल संचार संजाल.
he थी active in community अफेयर्स, औपनिवेशिक और state राजनीती, as well as नेशनल और अंतरराष्ट्रीय affairs.
इससे 1785 to 1788, he परोसा as राज्यपाल of पेन्सिलवेनिया.
toward the समाप्त of उसके जीवन, he freed his स्लेव और became one of the सबसे prominent abolitionists.
His colorful जीवन और legacy of वैज्ञानिक and political achievement, और औकात as एक of America 's सबसे influential Founding fathers, have seen Franklin सम्मानित on coinage और money ; warships ; the names of many towns, काउंटी, शैक्षणिक संस्थानों, namesakes, और कंपनियाँ ; और more than two सदियां बाद उसके death, countless सांस्कृतिक सन्दर्भ.

The श्रेणी follows a टोली of profilers इससे the FBI 's behavioral विश्लेषण ईकाई ( BAU ) based in Quantico, वर्जिनिया.
the bau is part of the एफबीआई National बीच for the विश्लेषण of Violent अपराधों.
the show differs इससे अनेक procedural dramas by focusing on प्रोफाइलिंग the दण्ड, rather than the crime itself.
the दिखाएँ is produced by the चिह्नित गॉर्डन Company in association with सीबीएस Television studios ( originally सर्वोपरि Network Television तब सीबीएस सर्वोपरि Network Television ) और एबीसी studios ( originally Touchstone टेलीविज़न ).

The orbital गति of a body, generally a ग्रह, a प्राकृतिक उपग्रह, an artificial उपग्रह, or a अनेक star, is the speed at which it orbits around the barycenter of a प्रणाली, प्रायः around a अधिक विशाल देह.
It can be प्रयुक्त to refer to either the mean कक्षीय गति, the औसत गति as it completes an कक्षा, or instantaneous orbital गति, the speed at a particular पाइंट in इसके कक्षा.
The orbital speed at कोई स्थिति in the orbit can be computed इससे the अलहदा to the सेंट्रल body at कि स्थिति, और the विशिष्ट कक्षीय उर्जा, जिससे is स्वतंत्र of position : the गतिज उर्जा is the कुल उर्जा minus the potential उर्जा.

Brown राजमहल होटल is the second-oldest operating होटल in डेनवर, Colorado और is एक of the first atrium-style होटल ever निर्मित.

dvd-video is a consumer वीडियो स्वरूप प्रयुक्त to स्टोर digital video on dvd discs, और is फिलहाल the dominant consumer वीडियो स्वरूप in Asia, North अमेरिका, यूरोपीय, और Australia.
discs using the dvd-video specification आवश्यकता a DVD ड्राइव और an h.262/mpeg-2 Part 2 डिकोडर ( e.g., a DVD player, or a कंप्यूटर dvd ड्राइव with a software dvd खिलाड़ी ).
वाणिज्यिक dvd फिल्मों are encoded using a संयोजन of H.262/MPEG-2 भाग 2 compressed वीडियो और audio of varying स्वरुप ( often multi-channel स्वरुप as वर्णित नीचे ).
typically, the data रेट लिये dvd फिल्मों सीमाएँ इससे 3 Mbit/s to 9.5 mbit/s, and the bit rate is प्रायः adaptive.
It was पहला उपलब्धियाँ लिये खुदरा around 1997.
the dvd-video specification थी created by dvd फ़ोरम and can be प्राप्त इससे DVD format/logo लाइसेंसिंग निगम लिये a fee of $ 5,000.
the specification is नहीं सरेआम उपलब्धियाँ, क्युकी every subscriber जरूर sign a non-disclosure agreement.
निश्चित सूचना in the dvd किताब is proprietary और गोपनीय.
the nautical मील ( प्रतीक M, nm or nmi ) is a ईकाई of लंबाई that is परिचय one मिनट of arc of अक्षांश measured साथ any मध्याह्न, or about one minute of arc of longitude at the equator.
By अंतरराष्ट्रीय अनुबंध it has been नियत at 1,852 metres exactly ( about 6,076 feet ).
it is a non- si ईकाई ( हालांकि accepted for use in the International प्रणाली of Units by the bipm ) प्रयुक्त विशेषकर by navigators in the शिपिंग और विमानन industries, and भी in ध्रुवीय खोजी.
it is commonly used in अंतरराष्ट्रीय विधि and treaties, विशेषकर regarding the हद of territorial waters.
it विकसित इससे the समुद्र मील और the सम्बन्धित भौगोलिक mile.
The nautical मील remains in use by समुद्र और एयर navigators worldwide क्युकी of इसके convenience जब working with charts.
सबसे nautical charts उपयोग the मर्केटर projection जिनकी scale varies by परिचय a फ़ैक्टर of छह from the equator to 80° अक्षांश, so चार्ट covering विशाल areas can not use a सिंगल रैखिक स्केल.
the nautical mile is nearly equal to a minute of अक्षांश on a chart, so a distance measured with a चार्ट divider can be roughly converted to nautical miles using the चार्ट 's अक्षांश स्केल.
Shippensburg is a borough in कम्बरलैंड और Franklin काउंटी in the u.S. state of पेन्सिलवेनिया.
settled in 1730, Shippensburg lies in the कम्बरलैंड घाटी, 41 मील ( 66 km ) west-southwest of Harrisburg, and is part of the Harrisburg– carlisle Metropolitan सांख्यिकीय क्षेत्रफल.
In 1900, 3,228 लोगों lived there ; in 1910, 3,457 ; and in 1940, 5,244 लोगों lived वहीँ.
The जनसांख्यिकी was 5,492 at the 2010 census.
shippensburg थी incorporated as a borough on जनवरी 21, 1819.
in the past, वहीँ were furniture कारखानों, engine and pump works, और अन्य औद्योगिक works located भीतर the कस्बा.

shippensburg is also घर to Shippensburg University of Pennsylvania, एक of 14 विश्वविद्यालयों of the पेन्सिलवेनिया State System of उच्चतर शिक्षा.
वार्षिक the पिछला full week of जुलाई, the shippensburg Community मेला is आयोजित.
begun in 1958, the मेला bills itself as Pennsylvania 's largest bi-county fair.
the fair includes agricultural दर्शाती, a शिल्प दिखाएँ, food vendors, और carnival यात्राएँ amongst अन्य बाते.
प्रत्येक गर्मियाँ on the last Saturday of अगस्त, Shippensburg holds the Corn पर्व, an इवेंट कि brings क्षेत्रीय artisans और विक्रेता to operate stands शहर.
The शहर is बंद to ट्रैफ़िक लिये at least 5 blocks लिये सबसे of the day.

ब्लैक बालदार जीभ ( BHT, also termed lingua villosa nigra ) refers to a कंडीशन of the जीभ where the filiform papillae elongate साथ black or brown discoloration, giving a ब्लैक और बालदार रूप.
The appearance may be alarming, लकिन it is a हानिरहित condition.

प्रबन्धन is by improving oral hygiene, विशेषकर scraping or brushing the tongue.
the IEEE 1394 interface is a सीरियल बस इंटरफ़ेस मानक for high-speed communications and isochronous real-time data transfer.
It was विकसित in the लेट 1980s और जल्दी 1990s by Apple, जो called it firewire.
The 1394 इंटरफ़ेस is comparable to USB, and often those two technologies हैं माना साथ, हालांकि usb रै अधिक मार्केट share.
Apple first included FireWire in some of its 1999 मॉडल, और सबसे ठहराना computers since the साल 2000 have शामिल firewire पोर्ट, हालांकि, as of 2013, nothing beyond the 800 संस्करण ( IEEE-1394b ).
the इंटरफ़ेस is also ज्ञात by the ब्रांड i.LINK ( सोनी ), and Lynx ( Texas यंत्र ).
आईईईई 1394 replaced parallel scsi in अनेक अनुप्रयोग, क्युकी of निम्नतर क्रियान्वयन लागत और a सरलीकृत, अधिक अनुकूलनीय cabling system.
the 1394 standard भी defines a backplane interface, though this is नहीं as widely प्रयुक्त.
आईईईई 1394 is the high-definition Audio-Video संजाल Alliance ( हाना ) मानक connection इंटरफ़ेस लिये A/V ( audio/visual ) component communication and control.
FireWire is also available in wireless, fiber ऑप्टिक, और समाक्षीय संस्करण using the isochronous प्रोटोकॉल.
स्टीफन `` Stevie '' रे vaughan ( अक्तूबर 3, 1954 – अगस्त 27, 1990 ) थी an अमरीकी guitarist, singer-songwriter, and रिकार्ड producer.
प्रायः referred to by his आद्याक्षर srv, Vaughan is बेहतरीन known as a founding सदस्य और leader of दोगुना ट्रबल.
साथ साथ वादक Chris Layton and bassist Tommy Shannon, वे ignited the blues पुनरुद्धार of the 1980s.
साथ a career spanning सात सालो, Vaughan और दोगुना ट्रबल consistently बेची out कॉन्सर्ट जबकि their एल्बम frequently गई सुनहरा.
He was born और raised in Dallas, टेक्सास, और लिये a छोटी period of समय जिया in ग्राहम, Texas.
As the younger brother of Jimmie Vaughan, vaughan प्रारंभ playing the गिटार at age seven और formed several bands that occasionally performed in लोकल nightclubs.
at age 17, he dropped out of high स्कूल and moved to ऑस्टिन to further pursue उसके musical करियर, joining समूह ऐसे as Krackerjack, the Nightcrawlers, and the cobras.
in 1977, he formed ट्रिपल Threat Revue, a बैंड कि आखिरकार विकसित into Double ट्रबल और regularly performed around Austin.
in 1982, Vaughan और दोगुना ट्रबल performed at the montreux Jazz Festival in स्विट्ज़रलैंड, catching the ध्यान of musicians दाउद बोवी और जैक्सन browne.
Bowie पूछा vaughan to खेल on his upcoming स्टुडियो album Let 's Dance, while Browne offered the band फ़्री उपयोग of his personal studio in लॉस Angeles to रिकार्ड an album.
in कूच 1983, Vaughan और Double Trouble were हस्ताक्षरित to एपिक Records by veteran रिकार्ड producer John हैमंड Sr. and released their debut album, Texas Flood in जून of कि साल.
After कामयाब touring, the समूह released the एल्बम, could n't स्टैंड the मौसम ( 1984 ) और आत्मा to Soul ( 1985 ), the latter of जिससे प्रदर्शित new keyboardist रीज़ wynans.
Although उसके करियर था progressed successfully, vaughan checked into a पुनर्वास हॉस्पिटल in अटलांटा, Georgia to give up a कोका और दारू आदत और लौटे to touring साथ the बैंड.
in June 1989, in कदम थी released और earned उन्हें a ग्रैमी पुरस्कार लिये बेहतरीन समकालीन Blues Performance.
on August 27, 1990, vaughan was killed in a helicopter crash following a प्रदर्शन in East ट्रॉय, विस्कॉन्सिन.
vaughan 's uniquely eclectic yet intense स्टाइल was निकला इससे a variety of musical जाति.
He थी बहकावे by blues musicians सहित अल्बर्ट किंग, फ्रेडी किंग, Otis Rush, and muddy Waters, और चट्टान guitarists ऐसे as Jimi Hendrix और Lonnie mack.
His गिटार playing reflected the क्लासिक blues और pentatonic तराजू.
He has received wide नाजुक मान्यता लिये उसके गिटार playing, ranking at # 6 on रोलिंग Stones list of `` 100 महानतम guitarists '' in 2011.
He थी posthumously inducted into the ब्लूज़ हॉल of Fame in 2000 और a memorial प्रतिमा was erected in ऑस्टिन 's ऑडिटोरियम shores पार्क.
स्टीवी रे vaughan is widely माना to be one of the महानतम संगीतकारों to आइये from the राज्य of टेक्सास.

in कंप्यूटर networking, gigabit Ethernet ( GbE or 1 gige ) is a पद describing various technologies for transmitting Ethernet फ्रेम्स at a रेट of a gigabit per दूसरी ( 1,000,000,000 बिट्स per दूसरी ), as पारिभाषित by the IEEE 802.3-2008 standard.
it came into उपयोग beginning in 1999, धीरे supplanting Fast ईथरनेट in तार local संजाल, where it performed considerably तेज़.
the केबल और उपकरण हैं बहुत समान to पिछला मानकों and were very आम और economical by 2010.
half-duplex gigabit कड़ी connected through hubs हैं allowed by the specification, लकिन full-duplex usage with switches is much अधिक common.

A postage stamp is a small टुकड़ा of paper कि is purchased और प्रदर्शित on an item of मेल as प्रमाण of भुगतान of postage.
Typically, stamps हैं बना from खास paper, with a national designation and denomination ( दाम ) on the face, और a गम चिपकने on the रिवर्स पक्ष.
postage stamps हैं खरीदा from a postal प्रशासन or other authorized विक्रेता और are used to अदा for the costs शामिल in चलती मेल as well as अन्य business necessities ऐसे as बीमे and registration.
the stamp’s shape is प्रायः कि of a छोटी आयताकार of varying proportions, हालांकि त्रिकोण or अन्य shapes हैं occasionally प्रयुक्त.
the स्टैम्प is affixed to an लिफाफा or अन्य डाक cover ( i.e., पैकेट, बक्सा, mailing बेलन ) कि the customer wishes to भेजें.
the item is तब processed by the postal प्रणाली, जहाँ a postmark, sometimes known as a रद्दीकरण चिह्नित, is प्रायः applied over the stamp और कवर ; this कार्यविधि marks the stamp as used, which रोकता इसके reuse.
the postmark indicates the तिथि and पाइंट of उत्पत्ति of the mailing.
The mailed मद is तब वितरित to the पता कि the customer has applied to the लिफाफा or कवर.
Postage stamps have facilitated the डिलीवरी of mail चूंकि the 1840s.
पहले इस time, ink और hand-stamps ( hence the word 'stamp ' ), usually बना इससे लकडी or cork, were often used to frank the मेल और confirm the भुगतान of postage.
The पहला adhesive postage स्टैम्प, commonly referred to as the Penny Black, थी जारी in the United किंगडम in 1840.
the invention of the stamp थी a भाग of the attempt to सुधार and improve the postal system in the संयुक्त Kingdom of ग्रेट Britain and आयरलैंड, जिससे in the early 19th सदी थी in अस्तव्यस्तता और rife साथ भ्रष्टाचार.
There are varying खाते of the आविष्कारक or inventors of the स्टैम्प.
पहले the परिचय of postage stamps, मेल in the uk was paid लिये by the प्राप्तकर्ता, a system कि was associated with an irresolvable प्रॉब्लम : the costs of delivering mail यहूद not recoverable by the डाक service जब recipients यहूद असमर्थ or unwilling to अदा लिये वितरित वस्तुएं, and प्रेषकों था no incentive to सीमित the क्रमांक, आकार, or weight of वस्तुएं भेजा, whether or not वे would ultimately be सशुल्क लिये.
The postage stamp resolved this समस्या in a सरल और सुरुचिपूर्ण manner, with the अतिरिक्त लाभ of room for an तत्व of beauty to be introduced.
बाद सम्बन्धित आविष्कारों शामिल डाक stationery ऐसे as prepaid-postage लिफाफे, post cards, lettercards, aerogrammes and wrappers, postage मीटर, and, अधिक recently, specialty boxes and लिफाफे provided फ़्री to the ग्राहक by the u.S. postal सेवा लिये priority or express mailing.
the postage stamp afforded convenience लिये both the मेलर and postal officials, more efficiently बरामद लागत लिये the postal service, and ultimately resulted in a बेहतर, faster डाक प्रणाली.
With the conveniences stamps offered, उनके उपयोग resulted in greatly increased mailings during the 19th और 20th सदियां.
postage stamps during इस era यहूद the most लोकप्रिय रास्ता of paying for मेल, लकिन by the end of the 20th century यहूद rapidly होने आत by the उपयोग of metered postage और बल्क mailing by व्यवसायों. )
the same परिणाम साथ आदर to communications by निजी parties occurred over the पिछला दशक of the 20th century और the first दशक of the 21st due to declining cost of long अलहदा telephone संचार and the development and explosive स्प्रेड of इलेक्ट्रॉनिक mailing ( `` e-mail '' via the Internet ) और bill paying प्रणालियों had.
As postage stamps साथ their engraved imagery began to appear on a फैली आधार, historians और collectors began to take notice.
The पढ़ाई of postage stamps and उनके उपयोग is referred to as philately.
Stamp collecting can be both a शौक and a रूप of historical study और सन्दर्भ, as government-issued postage stamps and their mailing प्रणालियों have always महरूम शामिल साथ the history of राष्ट्र.
the विश्वविद्यालयों of अलबामा at Birmingham ( uab ) is a पब्लिक विश्वविद्यालयों in Birmingham in the u.S. राज्य of अलबामा.
Developing इससे an एक्सटेंशन center established in 1936, the संस्था became an autonomous institution in 1969 और is आज एक of तीन संस्थानों in the University of Alabama प्रणाली.
UAB offers over 140 कार्यक्रम of पढ़ाई in 12 अकादमिक divisions leading to स्नातक 's, master 's, doctoral, और professional डिग्री in the सोशल और behavioral sciences, the liberal arts, कारोबार, शिक्षा, engineering, and health-related fields ऐसे as medicine, dentistry, optometry, नर्सिंग, और पब्लिक स्वास्थ्य.
the school is अत्यधिक renowned लिये its चिकित्सा शोध और प्राकृतिक sciences programs.
The UAB Health प्रणाली, one of the largest अकादमिक medical centers in the United राज्य, is संबद्ध साथ the university.

uab is the राज्य 's largest नियोक्ता, साथ अधिक than 18,000 संकाय and staff and over 53,000 कार्य at the विश्वविद्यालयों और in the स्वास्थ्य प्रणाली.
an अनुमानित 10 प्रतिशत of the कार्य in the birmingham-hoover महानगर क्षेत्रफल और 1 in 33 jobs in the state of Alabama are directly or indirectly सम्बन्धित to UAB.
the university 's overall सालाना economic impact was estimated to be $ 4.6 अरब in 2010.

Tofu, also called सेम दही, is a खाना बना by coagulating सोया रस और तब दबाने the resulting curds into soft white blocks.
it is a घटक in अनेक ईस्ट Asian और southeast Asian cuisines.
वहीँ are अनेक अलग किस्में of टोफू, सहित fresh tofu और टोफू कि has महरूम processed in some way.
टोफू रै a हल्का स्वाद और can be प्रयुक्त in savory और मीठी बर्तन.
It is often seasoned or marinated to suit the डिश.
Tofu originated in प्राचीन चीन some 2,000 सालो ago.
Chinese लेजेंड ascribes इसके invention to प्रिंस लियू an ( Chinese : 劉安 liú ān, 179–122 bc ).
Tofu and इसके उत्पादन तकनीक यहूद introduced into Korea and तब जापानी दौरान the Nara काल.
it स्प्रेड into अन्य भाग of ईस्ट Asia as well.
इस spread संभावित coincided साथ the स्प्रेड of Buddhism क्युकी it is an महत्वपूर्ण source of प्रोटीन in the शाकाहारी आहार of ईस्ट एशियाई Buddhism.
li shizhen in the मिंग राजवंश वर्णित a method of बनाना टोफू in bencao gangmu.
टोफू रै a कम calorie गिनती, अपेक्षाकृत विशाल amounts of protein, and छोटी fat.
it is ऊँची in आयरन and depending on the coagulant प्रयुक्त in manufacturing, may भी be ऊँची in calcium and/or magnesium.
बुलबुले ( born 1983 ) is a common chimpanzee, known for being the one-time पालतु of अमरीकी रिकॉर्डिंग artist माइकल जैक्सन, who खरीदा the primate इससे a टेक्सास research facility in the जल्दी 1980s.
the एनिमल was a बारंबार सफर companion to the singer, जिनकी अनुलग्नक to the एनिमल led to media mockery and, among other कारकों, to a पब्लिक बोध of जैक्सन as an eccentric.
दौरान the ख़राब World Tour, for example, जैक्सन brought बुलबुले साथ उसे to जापानी, जहाँ वे दोनो पिया tea with the महापौर of ओसाका.
Bubbles थी initially kept at the जैक्सन family 's घर in encino, Los Angeles, लकिन थी स्थानांतरित to neverland ranch in 1988.

bloemfontein (, ; डच लिये `` fountain of पुष्प '' ) is the पूंजी नगर of the फ़्री राज्य Province of दक्षिण Africa ; और, as the judicial पूंजी of the स्वदेश, एक of दक्षिण अफ़्रीकी 's तीन नेशनल capitals – the अन्य two होने Cape Town, the विधान पूंजी, and Pretoria, the प्रशासनिक पूंजी.
bloemfontein is popularly और poetically ज्ञात as `` the नगर of roses ``, owing to the प्रचुरता of ये पुष्प और the annual रोज़ पर्व आयोजित वहीँ.

Bloemfontein is situated on शुष्क घासभूमि at, at an altitude of ऊपर समुद्र level.
The नगर is घर to 369,568 residents, जबकि the mangaung लोकल नगरपालिका has a population of 645,455.

The अर्थ of जीवन is a philosophical question concerning the significance of जीवन or अस्तित्व in सामान्य.
it can भी be expressed in different forms, ऐसे as `` Why are we here ? ``, `` What is जीवन सब about ? ``, and `` What is the purpose of existence ? ''
it has महरूम the subject of much philosophical, scientific, और theological अटकलें throughout इतिहास.
There have महरूम a विशाल क्रमांक of प्रस्तावित answers to these questions इससे many different cultural और वैचारिक पृष्ठभूमि.
the अर्थ of life is in the philosophical और religious conceptions of existence, सोशल ties, चेतना, and happiness, और borders on अनेक other मुद्दे, such as सांकेतिक meaning, सत्तामीमांसा, value, purpose, आचार, शुभ और evil, फ़्री will, the अस्तित्व of एक or अनेक देवताओं, conceptions of परमेश्वर, the आत्मा, and the आफ्टरलाइफ.
वैज्ञानिक contributions फ़ोकस primarily on describing सम्बन्धित अनुभवजन्य तथ्य परिचय the ब्रह्मांड, exploring the context और पैरामीटर्स concerning the 'how ' of life.
विज्ञान also अध्ययन and can provide सुझाव for the pursuit of well-being और a सम्बन्धित conception of नैतिकता.
An वैकल्पिक, humanistic दृष्टिकोण poses the question `` कया is the meaning of my life ? ''
the value of the question pertaining to the purpose of life may coincide साथ the achievement of परम वास्तविकता, or a अहसास of oneness, or भी a feeling of sacredness.
