`` the Princess और the Pea '' ( ; शाब्दिक अनुवाद : `` the राजकुमारी on the मटर '' ) is a literary परी टेल by hans Christian andersen about a यंग woman whose royal पहचान is स्थापित by a परीक्षण of उसके शारीरिक sensitivity.
the टेल थी first प्रकाशित साथ तीन अन्य by andersen in an inexpensive पुस्तिका on 8 May 1835 in कोपेनहेगन by c.a. reitzel.
andersen था सुना the स्टोरी as a child, and it संभावित has its source in लोक सामग्री, possibly originating इससे Sweden as it is अनजान in the Danish oral परंपरा.
neither `` the राजकुमारी and the मटर '' nor andersen 's अन्य किस्से of 1835 were खूब received by Danish critics, जो disliked their casual, chatty स्टाइल, और उनके कमी of नैतिकता.
in 1959 `` the राजकुमारी और the मटर '' was adapted to the musical स्टेज in a production पुकारा एकबार Upon a Mattress अभिनीत Carol burnett.
जर्मनी अमेरिकी ( ) are citizens of the संयुक्त States who यहूद either born in Germany or are of जर्मनी ancestry.
वे comprise परिचय 50 लाख people, बनाना them the largest ancestry समूह ahead of आयरिश अमेरिकी, अफ़्रीकी अमेरिकी और अंग्रेज़ी Americans.
वे comprise परिचय 1/3 of the जर्मनी diaspora all over the संसार.
none of the जर्मनी states था नई संसार colonies.
Not जबतक the 1670s किया the first significant groups of German आप्रवासियों arrive in the अंग्रेजों colonies, settling primarily in New York and पेन्सिलवेनिया.
आव्रजन जारी in very large numbers दौरान the 19th century, with कुछ आठ million आमद from Germany.
वे यहूद खींचा by the attractions of land और धार्मिक स्वतंत्रता, and pushed out of यूरोपीय by shortages of land और religious or राजनैतिक oppression.
अनेक arrived seeking धार्मिक or political स्वतंत्रता, others लिये economic opportunities greater than those in यूरोपीय, और अन्य simply लिये the chance to प्रारंभ भैस in the New World.
the आमद पहले 1850 यहूद ज़्यादातर farmers जो sought आउट the most productive land, where उनके intensive खेती तकनीकों would pay बंद.
बाद 1840, many आए to शहरों, जहाँ `` germania '' —german-speaking districts—soon उभरा.
जर्मनी Americans स्थापित the पहला kindergartens in the संयुक्त राज्य, introduced the क्रिसमस पेड़ tradition, and originated popular अमरीकी foods such as hot dogs और hamburgers.
जर्मनी अमरीकी celebrations हैं आयोजित throughout the country, one of the सबसे well-known being the german-american Steuben परेड in नई यॉर्क City, आयोजित प्रत्येक third शनिवार in सितंबर.
There are also major सालाना events in Chicago, सिनसिनाटी, मिल्वौकी, Pittsburgh, st. Louis और other cities.
जैसे अनेक other आप्रवासियों कि आए to the संयुक्त राज्य, an overwhelming क्रमांक of लोगों of German or partial German descent have essentially become Americanized.
The Preamble to the संयुक्त States Constitution is a ब्रैड परिचयात्मक statement of the Constitution 's fundamental उद्देश्य and guiding सिद्धान्त.
It states in general शर्तें, and courts have referred to it as विश्वसनीय evidence of, the founding Fathers ' intentions regarding the Constitution 's अर्थ और कया वे hoped the संविधान would achieve as it pertains to सब of the people of the संयुक्त States.
as the phrase, `` we the people '' suggests that the नई सरकारी originates इससे the लोगों of the United States और it सेट into motion a question as it pertains to कि विशाल जनसांख्यिकी concerning the individual अधिकारों और equality among सब people ; this can be seen सबसे broadly in the divide between republicanism and social democracy.
the इतिहास of the अंतरजाल began साथ the development of electronic कंप्यूटर in the 1950s.
the पब्लिक was first introduced to the concepts कि would सीसे to the Internet when a message was भेजा over the ARPANet इससे computer विज्ञान Professor लियोनार्ड kleinrock 's प्रयोगशाला at विश्वविद्यालयों of कैलिफ़ोर्निया, Los एंजिल्स ( ucla ), बाद the दूसरी टुकड़ा of network उपकरण थी installed at Stanford Research संस्थान ( श्री ).
Packet switched networks such as ARPANET, Mark i at npl in the uk, cyclades, मेरिट संजाल, tymnet, और telenet, यहूद developed in the लेट 1960s और early 1970s using a किस्में of protocols.
the arpanet in particular led to the विकास of प्रोटोकॉल लिये internetworking, in which अनेक separate networks could be joined साथ into a network of networks.
in 1982, the Internet प्रोटोकॉल सुइट ( TCP/IP ) थी मानकीकृत, and consequently, the अवधारणा of a world-wide network of interconnected tcp/ip networks, पुकारा the अंतरजाल, थी introduced.
Access to the arpanet was expanded in 1981 जब the नेशनल Science न्यास ( NSF ) विकसित the कंप्यूटर विज्ञान संजाल ( CSNET ) and again in 1986 when nsfnet provided अभिगम to supercomputer sites in the संयुक्त States इससे research और education organizations.
वाणिज्यिक Internet सेवा providers ( isps ) began to emerge in the late 1980s and जल्दी 1990s.
the ARPANET was decommissioned in 1990.
the Internet थी commercialized in 1995 जब nsfnet थी decommissioned, निकालना the पिछला प्रतिबंध on the उपयोग of the अंतरजाल to carry वाणिज्यिक traffic.
Since the mid-1990s, the अंतरजाल रै था a revolutionary impact on संस्कृति and कॉमर्स, including the rise of near-instant संचार by इलेक्ट्रॉनिक मेल, तत्काल messaging, Voice over अंतरजाल Protocol ( VoIP ) `` फोन काल्स '', two-way इंटरैक्टिव video calls, और the World Wide वेब with its discussion forums, blogs, सोशल नेटवर्किंग, और online shopping sites.
the शोध और education जातियाँ continues to develop and उपयोग advanced संजाल such as NSF 's very ऊँची गति रीढ़ Network Service ( vbns ), internet2, और नेशनल LambdaRail.
increasing amounts of data हैं transmitted at higher and उच्चतर speeds over रेशा ऑप्टिक संजाल ऑपरेटिंग at 1-gbit/s, 10-gbit/s, or अधिक.
The Internet 's takeover over the वैश्विक संचार लैंडस्केप थी लगभग instant in ऐतिहासिक शर्तें : it तभी communicated 1 % of the सूचना बहती through two-way दूरसंचार संजाल in the साल 1993, already 51 % by 2000, and अधिक than 97 % of the telecommunicated सूचना by 2007.
Today the Internet continues to grow, चलित by कभी greater amounts of ऑनलाइन सूचना, कॉमर्स, entertainment, and social networking.
दक्षिणपश्चिम Airlines co. ( ) is a major U.S. एयरलाइन और the world 's largest low-cost वाहक, headquartered in डलास, टेक्सास.
It थी स्थापित in 1967 और अपनाया its वर्तमान नाम in 1971.
the airline has अधिक than 46,000 कर्मचारी और operates more than 3,400 फ़्लाइट प्रति day.
as of जून 5, 2011, it carries the सबसे domestic passengers of कोई u.S. airline.
As of April 2013, दक्षिणपश्चिम एयरलाइंस रै scheduled service to 84 destinations in 41 राज्य and Puerto Rico.
Southwest एयरलाइंस रै solely संचालित Boeing 737s, except for a few सालो in the 1970s और 1980s, when it संचालित Boeing 727s.

On कूच 1, 2012, the कम्पनी थी issued a सिंगल operating प्रमाणपत्र, technically becoming one airline.

बेनेडिक्ट xvi (,, ; born जोसेफ aloisius ratzinger on 16 अप्रैल 1927 ) is Pope emeritus of the कैथोलिक Church.
he परोसा as पोप from 2005 to 2013.
In that स्थिति, he थी both the leader of the कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर और sovereign of the Vatican नगर State.
Benedict थी निर्वाचित on 19 अप्रैल 2005 in a papal conclave, मनाये his papal Inauguration Mass on 24 अप्रैल 2005, और took possession of his cathedral, the archbasilica of st. John lateran, on 7 may 2005.
ordained as a पुजारी in 1951 in उसके देशी Bavaria, ratzinger स्थापित himself as a अत्यधिक regarded university theologian by the late 1950s and was नियुक्त a पूरा professor in 1958.
बाद a long career as an अकादमिक, सेवारत as a प्राध्यापक of धर्मशास्त्र at अनेक German universities—the पिछला होने the विश्वविद्यालयों of Regensburg, जहाँ he परोसा as वाइस अध्यक्ष of the university in 1976 और 1977—he was appointed archbishop of म्यूनिख और Freising और कार्डिनल by Pope Paul vi in 1977, an असामान्य प्रमोशन लिये someone साथ छोटी लुभावने अनुभव.
In 1981, he settled in रोम when he became prefect of the सभा लिये the doctrine of the Faith, one of the most महत्वपूर्ण dicasteries of the Roman curia.
इससे 2002 until उसके election as pope, he was also Dean of the College of कार्डिनल्स, और as such, the प्राइमस inter pares among the कार्डिनल्स.
prior to becoming pope, he थी `` a प्रमुख figure on the वेटिकन stage for a क्वार्टर of a century '' as `` एक of the सबसे respected, influential and विवादास्पद सदस्यों of the College of कार्डिनल्स '' ; he था an influence `` दूसरी to none when it came to सेटिंग church प्राथमिकताएं and दिशानिर्देश '' as one of Pope जॉन पॉल ii 's closest confidants.
he थी originally a उदार theologian, but adopted रूढ़िवादी दृश्य after 1968.
उसके सफल कृतियाँ defend परंपरागत कैथोलिक doctrine and values.
दौरान his papacy, Benedict xvi advocated a वापसी to आधारभूत Christian मान to काउंटर the increased secularisation of many पश्चिमी देशों.
he views relativism 's denial of objective सच्चाई, और the denial of moral truths in particular, as the central problem of the 21st century.
he taught the importance of both the कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर और an understanding of परमेश्वर 's redemptive love.
पोप बेनेडिक्ट also revived a क्रमांक of परंपराओं including elevating the tridentine Mass to a more prominent position.
he नवीनीकृत the relationship between the Catholic गिरिजाघर और आर्ट, viewing the उपयोग of सौंदर्य as a पाथ to the sacred, promoted the use of लैटिन, और reintroduced traditional papal garments, लिये जिससे कारण he थी पुकारा `` the pope of aesthetics ''.
he रै महरूम described as `` the प्रमुख बौद्धिक force in the Church '' चूंकि the mid-1980s.
अनेक of पोप बेनेडिक्ट 's students इससे उसके अकादमिक career are also prominent churchmen आज और confidantes of him, notably क्रिस्टोफ schönborn.
on 11 February 2013, पोप Benedict घोषित his इस्तीफा in a वाक in लैटिन पहले the cardinals, citing a `` कमी of शक्ति of mind and देह '' due to his उन्नत age.
His resignation became प्रभावी on 28 फ़रवरी 2013.
He is the first पोप to resign चूंकि पोप ग्रेगरी XII in 1415, and the पहला to do so on उसके अपना initiative चूंकि पोप celestine v in 1294.
as पोप emeritus, Benedict retains the style of His पवित्रता, और the title of पोप, and होगा continue to पोशाक in the papal रंग of white.
he was succeeded by पोप फ्रांसिस on 13 कूच 2013, और he moved into the newly renovated Mater Ecclesiae monastery for his रिटायरमेंट on 2 May 2013..

A बहुत early चित्रण of लोगों using a stereoscope.
stereoscopy ( also पुकारा stereoscopics or 3D imaging ) is a technique लिये बनाना or बढ़ाना the illusion of गहराई in an image by means of stereopsis लिये binocular दृष्टि.
The शब्द stereoscopy derives इससे the यूनानी `` στερεός '' ( stereos ), `` कड़, ठोस '' + `` σκοπέω '' ( skopeō ), `` to look '', `` to देखिए ''.
सबसे stereoscopic विधि उपस्थित दो ऑफसेट images separately to the left और सही eye of the दर्शक.
ये two-dimensional बिंब हैं then combined in the दिमाग to दे the perception of 3D depth.
This technique is विशिष्ट from 3D displays that display an चित्र in तीन पूरा आयाम, allowing the observer to increase सूचना परिचय the 3-dimensional वस्तुएँ being प्रदर्शित by head and eye आंदोलनों.
जॉन Adams ( October 30, 1735 ( o.s. October 19, 1735 ) – जुलाई 4, 1826 ) was the second अध्यक्ष of the संयुक्त राज्य ( 1797–1801 ), having पहले परोसा as the first vice अध्यक्ष of the United States.
an अमरीकी founding Father, he was a statesman, राजनयिक, और a leading एडवोकेट of अमरीकी independence from ग्रेट ब्रिटेन.
खूब educated, he was an Enlightenment political theorist जो promoted republicanism और wrote prolifically about his प्रायः seminal विचार, दोनो in प्रकाशित works और in letters to his बीवी और key adviser अबीगैल as खूब as to other Founding Fathers.
एडम्स आए to prominence in the जल्दी stages of the अमरीकी क्रान्ति.
a वकील और पब्लिक फिगर in Boston, as a प्रतिनिधि इससे Massachusetts to the महाद्वीपीय कॉंग्रेस, he played a अग्रणी role in persuading कॉंग्रेस to declare स्वतंत्रता.
He assisted थामस Jefferson in drafting the घोषणा of स्वतंत्रता in 1776, और was its primary advocate in the Congress.
बाद, as a diplomat in Europe, he helped negotiate the eventual सलाम सन्धि with Great Britain, और थी responsible for obtaining vital सरकारी लोन इससे एम्सटर्डम bankers.
a राजनैतिक theorist और इतिहासकार, Adams largely wrote the मैसाचुसेट्स Constitution in 1780, which together साथ his पहले Thoughts on सरकारी, बहकावे American राजनैतिक विचार.
एक of his महानतम भूमिकाएँ was as a judge of अक्षर : in 1775, he मनोनीत George वॉशिंगटन to be commander-in-chief, और 25 years बाद मनोनीत जॉन मार्शल to be Chief Justice of the United राज्य.
Adams ' revolutionary श्रेय secured उसे दो terms as George Washington 's वाइस अध्यक्ष और उसके अपना election in 1796 as the second अध्यक्ष.
दौरान उसके one term, he encountered ferocious हमले by the jeffersonian republicans, as खूब as the प्रबल faction in उसके अपना Federalist Party led by his कड़वा दुश्मन सिकंदर हैमिल्टन.
एडम्स हस्ताक्षरित the विवादास्पद एलियन and राजद्रोह अधिनियमों, and निर्मित up the army and नेवी especially in the फेस of an undeclared नवल युद्ध ( पुकारा the `` quasi-war `` ) साथ France, 1798–1800.
The प्रमुख accomplishment of his प्रेसिडेंसी was उसके शांतिपूर्ण रेज़ोल्यूशन of the विरोध in the face of हैमिल्टन 's विपक्ष.
In 1800, एडम्स थी defeated लिये re-election by Thomas जेफरसन और रिटायर्ड to मैसाचुसेट्स.
he later resumed उसके दोस्ती साथ जेफरसन.
He and उसके बीवी, अबीगैल एडम्स, founded an संपन्नता family लकीर of politicians, राजनयिकों, और historians अभी referred to as the एडम्स political family.
एडम्स थी the father of John क्विंसी Adams, the छठे President of the United राज्य.
His achievements have received greater मान्यता in modern टाइम्स, हालांकि his contributions यहूद not initially as मनाये as those of other Founders.
एडम्स थी the पहला u.S. अध्यक्ष to reside in the building that आखिरकार became known as the श्वेत हाउस.
the संयुक्त राज्य ten-dollar विधेयक ( $ 10 ) is a denomination of United States currency.
the पहला u.S. सचिव of the राजकोष ( 1789–95 ), सिकंदर हैमिल्टन, is currently featured on the obverse of the bill, जबकि the u.S. राजकोष भवन is featured on the रिवर्स.
( हैमिल्टन is एक of दो non-presidents featured on फिलहाल issued u.S. बिल्स.
the other is बेंजामिन Franklin, on the $ 100 bill.
हैमिल्टन is एक of तभी four लोगों प्रदर्शित on u.S. paper करेंसी ( 1861 to the उपस्थित ) who थी not born in the महाद्वीपीय संयुक्त राज्य, as he थी इससे the वेस्ट Indies.
The others हैं : Albert gallatin, Switzerland ( $ 500 1862/63 विधिक Tender ) ; George Meade, Spain ( $ 1,000 1890/91 Treasury Note ) ; and Robert मॉरिस, इंग्लैण्ड ( $ 1,000 1862/63 विधिक टेंडर ; $ 10 1878/80 चांदी प्रमाणपत्र ).
In जोड, kamehameha I, appears on the 2008 Hawaii राज्य क्वार्टर. )
सब $ 10 बिल्स जारी आज are संघीय Reserve Notes.
the Bureau of Engraving और Printing says the औसत जीवन of a $ 10 विधेयक in परिसंचरण is 18 महीने before it is replaced due to पहनें.
लगभग 6 % of all us banknotes मुद्रित in 2009 were $ 10 बिल्स.
टेन डालर bills हैं delivered by Federal Reserve बैंको in पीला straps.

The $ 10 bill is the only U.S. paper currency in परिसंचरण in जिससे the पोर्ट्रेट चेहरों to the left ( the $ 100,000 विधेयक प्रदर्शित a पोर्ट्रेट of Woodrow Wilson facing to the left, लकिन was प्रयुक्त only for intra-government transactions ).

A jetboat is a नाव propelled by a जेट of जल ejected इससे the वापस of the शिल्प.
नापसंद a powerboat or motorboat that उपयोग a propeller in the water below or पीछे the boat, a jetboat draws the water इससे under the boat into a pump inside the नाव, तब expels it through a nozzle at the stern.
jetboats यहूद originally designed by सर William Hamilton ( जो विकसित a waterjet in 1954 ) for आपरेशन in the fast-flowing और उथले rivers of New Zealand, specifically to overcome the प्रॉब्लम of propellers striking rocks in such waters.
पिछला attempts at waterjet propulsion था very छोटी lifetimes, generally due to the inefficient डिज़ाइन of the इकाई और the फैक्ट कि they offered few advantages over conventional propellers.
नापसंद these पिछला waterjet developments, ऐसे as campini 's and the hanley hydrojet, Hamilton था a specific need for a नोदन प्रणाली to operate in very-shallow जल, and the waterjet proved to be the ideal solution.
From इस, the popularity of the जेट ईकाई और jetboat increased rapidly.
Through further developments, it थी मिला the waterjet offered अनेक other लाभ over propellers लिये a wide range of पोत types, और as ऐसे, waterjets हैं used widely आज लिये अनेक high-speed बरतन, सहित यात्री ferries, बचाव craft, patrol नौकाएँ and offshore supply बरतन.
jetboats हैं अत्यधिक maneuverable, and अनेक can, from full गति, be reversed और brought to a stop भीतर little अधिक than उनके अपना लंबाई, in a maneuver ज्ञात as a `` crash रोकें ''.
The खूब ज्ञात हैमिल्टन turn or `` jet spin '' is a high-speed maneuvre where the boat 's इंजन throttle is cut, the परिचालन is turned sharply और the throttle खोली again, causing the boat to spin जल्दी around with a विशाल स्प्रे of जल.
वहीँ is no engineering limit to the आकार of jetboats, though the validity of their उपयोग depends a लॉट on the प्रकार of application.
क्लासिक prop-drives are generally अधिक efficient और economical at low speeds, up to परिचय, लकिन as नाव गति increases beyond this, the अतिरिक्त hull resistance उत्पन्न by struts, rudders, shafts ( इत्यादि. ) means waterjets हैं more कुशल in the 20-50 गांठ दायरा ( up to ).
भी, in परिस्थितियों साथ very विशाल propellers turning at slow speeds ( ऐसे as tug boats ), the equivalent आकार waterjet would be too बिग to be व्यावहारिक.
लिये ये reasons, the vast बहुमत of waterjet units are संस्थापित in high-speed vessels और in particular परिस्थितियों where उथले draught, maneuverability, और load flexibility हैं प्रमुख concerns.
The biggest jet-driven बरतन हैं मिला in military use or the high-speed passenger/car ferry उद्योग.
दक्षिण Africa 's s ( लगभग long ) हैं the biggest jet-propelled बरतन so दूर.
Even ये German-built बरतन are सक्षम of performing `` क्रैश stops ''.
Uveitis is broadly defined as inflammation of the uvea.
The uvea consists of the मध्य, pigmented, vascular structures of the eye और शामिल the आईरिस, ciliary देह, and choroid.
uveitis requires an तात्कालिक referral and thorough examination by an ophthalmologist or optometrist along साथ तात्कालिक उपचार to control the सूजन.

the film is based on the स्टीफन किंग अनोखा The जगमगाता.
a लेखक, Jack Torrance, takes a job as an off-season caretaker at an isolated होटल.
उसके young बेटे possesses मानसिक abilities और is समर्थ to see बाते इससे the past and भविष्य, ऐसे as the भूत जो inhabit the hotel.
जल्द बाद settling in, the परिवार is trapped in the होटल by a snowstorm, और जोकर धीरे becomes influenced by a अलौकिक उपस्थिति ; he उतरता into दीवानगी and कोशिशें to murder उसके बीवी और बेटे.
Unlike previous Kubrick films, which developed an audience gradually by भवन on word-of-mouth, the जगमगाता थी released as a mass-market फिल्मी, खोलने at first in बस दो शहरों on मेमोरियल दिन, तब देशभर a month बाद.
Although आरंभिक response to the फिल्मी थी मिश्रित, बाद critical assessment थी अधिक favorable और it is अभी viewed as a क्लासिक of the हॉरर विधा.
Film director Martin स्कोर्सेसे, writing in The Daily जानवर, ranked it as एक of the 11 scariest horror movies of सब समय.
Film आलोचकों, फिल्मी विद्यार्थी, और kubrick 's producer, Jan harlan, have remarked on the enormous influence the फिल्मी has था on लोकप्रिय culture.

आँगन आहार Cola थी a ब्रांड of diet सोडा introduced by पेप्सी in 1963.

This स्वाद लकीर was नहीं meant to compete with ब्रांड्स जैसे नारंगी crush, but बल्कि भरण आउट the line.

Advertising लिये आँगन was comparatively scarce ; at the समय, bottlers were regionally franchised, और सम्बन्धित advertising was necessarily local.

अवसंरचना is basic physical और organizational structures needed लिये the आपरेशन of a society or enterprise, or the सेवाएं and सुविधाएं necessary लिये an economy to फलन.
it can be generally पारिभाषित as the नियत of interconnected संरचनात्मक तत्व कि provide फ्रेमवर्क supporting an entire structure of विकास.
It is an महत्वपूर्ण term लिये judging a country or region 's development.
The term typically refers to the technical structures कि support a समाज, ऐसे as सड़कें, bridges, जल सप्लाई, sewers, electrical ग्रिड, telecommunications, and so forth, और can be पारिभाषित as `` the physical components of interrelated systems providing commodities और सेवाएं essential to enable, sustain, or बढ़ाएँ societal living शर्तें. ''
viewed functionally, अवसंरचना facilitates the उत्पादन of goods और सेवाएं, and भी the वितरण of finished उत्पाद to बाज़ार, as खूब as मौलिक सोशल services such as schools and अस्पताल ; for उदाहरण, सड़कें enable the हस्तांतरण of कच्चा materials to a फैक्टरी.
in सैन्य parlance, the term refers to the इमारतें and स्थाई installations जरुरी for the support, redeployment, और operation of सैन्य forces.
to मेक it सरल, infrastructure is anything कि is needed everyday, an रोज मद.

mitochondrial डीएनए.
इंसान genetic variation is the जेनेटिक differences both भीतर और among populations.
वहीँ may be अनेक विसंगतियाँ of कोई given जीन in the human जनसांख्यिकी ( जीनों ), leading to polymorphism.
अनेक जीनों are नहीं बहुरूपी, meaning कि only a सिंगल allele is उपस्थित in the population : the जीन is then said to be fixed.
no दो इंसानो हैं genetically एकसमान.
Even monozygotic twins, who develop इससे एक zygote, have infrequent जेनेटिक differences due to mutations occurring during development और gene नक़ल क्रमांक variation.
Differences between individuals, भी closely related individuals, हैं the कुंजी to तकनीकों ऐसे as जेनेटिक fingerprinting.
Alleles occur at अलग frequencies in different इंसान populations, साथ populations that are more geographically and ancestrally रिमोट tending to differ अधिक.
कल्याणकारी of मतभेद between individuals शामिल the एक्सचेंज of genes दौरान meiosis और विभिन्न mutational events.
वहीँ are at तनिक two reasons why genetic variation exists between populations.
प्राकृतिक चयन may confer an adaptive लाभ to individuals in a विशिष्ट पर्यावरण if an allele provides a प्रतिस्पर्धी लाभ.
alleles under चयन are संभावित to occur only in those भौगोलिक regions जहाँ they confer an लाभ.
the दूसरी main कारण of genetic variation is due to the ऊँची degree of neutrality of सबसे mutations.
सबसे mutations do नहीं appear to have कोई selective प्रभाव एक way or the other on the organism.
The main cause is जेनेटिक drift, this is the effect of random परिवर्तन in the जीन pool.
In humans, संस्थापक प्रभाव और पास्ट small जनसांख्यिकी size ( increasing the likelihood of जेनेटिक बहाव ) may have had an महत्वपूर्ण influence in neutral मतभेद between populations.
the theory कि इंसानो recently migrated आउट of Africa supports this.
the पढ़ाई of human जेनेटिक variation has दोनो विकासवादी significance और चिकित्सा applications.
It can सहायता वैज्ञानिकों समझे ancient इंसान जनसांख्यिकी migrations as खूब as कैसा अलग इंसान समूह are biologically सम्बन्धित to एक another.
लिये medicine, study of human genetic विभिन्नता may be महत्वपूर्ण because कुछ disease-causing alleles occur अधिक often in लोगों इससे विशिष्ट भौगोलिक regions.
नई findings दिखाएँ कि each इंसान रै on औसत 60 new mutations compared to उनके अभिभावक.
Apart इससे mutations, many genes कि may have aided इंसानो in प्राचीन टाइम्स plague humans आज.
लिये उदाहरण, it is suspected that जीनों कि allow humans to अधिक efficiently प्रक्रम खाना हैं those that मेक लोगों susceptible to मोटापा and diabetes आज.
Tea Party प्रदर्शनकारियों on the West Lawn of the u.S. Capitol और the नेशनल Mall at the Taxpayer March on Washington on सितंबर 12, 2009.
the Tea पार्टी गति is an अमरीकी राजनैतिक movement कि अधिवक्ताओं strict adherence to the संयुक्त States Constitution, reducing u.S. सरकारी spending and taxes, and reduction of the u.S. नेशनल कर्ज़ और संघीय बजट deficit.
the गति रै been called partly रूढ़िवादी, partly libertarian, और partly populist.
the movement has प्रायोजित protests and समर्थित राजनैतिक उम्मीदवार चूंकि 2009.
The नाम of the गति is derived इससे the Boston चाय पार्टी of 1773, an iconic इवेंट in American इतिहास.
anti-tax protesters in the United राज्य have प्रायः referred to the original Boston चाय पार्टी for प्रेरणा.
सन्दर्भ to the बोस्टन चाय Party यहूद part of कर दिन विरोध आयोजित throughout the 1990s और earlier.

The मुद्राएँ of प्यूर्टो Rico closely follow the ऐतिहासिक development of प्यूर्टो Rico.
As a colony of Spain और the संयुक्त राज्य, Puerto Rico थी granted the use of both विदेशी और provincial currencies.
Following the स्पेनी colonization in 1502, Puerto Rico became an महत्वपूर्ण बंदरगाहों, with इसके अपना सप्लाई of gold.
however, as the खनिज reserves भागा empty within the सदी, the द्वीपसमूह 's अर्थव्यवस्था suffered.
the Spanish क्राउन जारी the situado mexicano, जिससे meant that a semi-regular शिपमेंट of सुनहरा इससे the viceroyalty of नई स्पेन होता be भेजा to the island, as a way to provide आर्थिक support.
Between 1636 and 1637, Philip iv of Spain imposed a tax which था to be सशुल्क using a आय stamp.
प्रेरित by इस, प्यूर्टो रीको began producing banknotes in 1766, बनने the पहला उपनिवेश to छपाई 8- real banknotes in the स्पेनी Empire और which in the Spanish सरकारी 's स्वीकृति of subsequent मुद्दे.
the situado थी discontinued दौरान the 19th सदी, creating an economic crisis, as a result of मैक्सिको gaining इसके स्वतंत्रता इससे स्पेन.
साल्वाडोर meléndez bruna, the colonial राज्यपाल in दफ्तर, ordered the समस्या of प्रांतीय banknotes, बनाना the Puerto rican peso.
however, printing of ये banknotes ceased बाद 1815.
During the following दशकों, विदेशी coins became the फैली करेंसी.
in the 1860s and 1870s, banknotes reemerged.
on फ़रवरी 1, 1890, the banco español de Puerto रीको थी inaugurated और began issuing banknotes.
the बैंको designed चार श्रेणी और लगाई three in circulation under स्पेनी नियम.
In 1895, a royal डिक्री ordered the उत्पादन of प्रांतीय पेसो सिक्के.
on अगस्त 13, 1898, the spanish-american युद्ध ended साथ स्पेन ceding Puerto Rico to the United राज्य.
The Banco español de प्यूर्टो रीको was renamed बैंको of पोर्टो रीको and जारी बिल्स समतुल्य to the संयुक्त राज्य डालर, बनाना the Puerto rican dollar.
in 1902, the पहला National बैंको of Porto Rico जारी banknotes in a समानांतर manner.
दो more श्रेणी यहूद जारी until 1913.
After प्यूर्टो Rico 's economy and मौद्रिक प्रणाली थी fully एकीकृत into the संयुक्त States ' आर्थिक and मौद्रिक प्रणाली, the प्यूर्टो Rican dollars यहूद redeemed लिये those जारी by the United States राजकोष.
The peso and dollar have महरूम followed by other समकालीन issues, सहित commemorative banknotes, private currency, and a क्वार्टर सिक्का designed साथ फोर्ट सैन Felipe डेल Morro in the face.

Cancer, known medically as a malignant फुलाव, is a व्यापक group of विभिन्न diseases, सब involving unregulated कोशिका विकास.
In कर्कट, cells divide और grow uncontrollably, forming malignant tumors, and invade आसपास भाग of the देह.
the cancer may भी स्प्रेड to more दूर भाग of the body through the lymphatic प्रणाली or bloodstream.
नहीं सब tumors are cancerous.
benign tumors do नहीं grow uncontrollably, do नहीं invade neighboring ऊतकों, और do नहीं spread throughout the देह.
वहीँ are over 200 अलग ज्ञात cancers कि afflict humans.
Determining कया causes cancer is complex.
अनेक बाते हैं ज्ञात to बढ़ाएँ the risk of cancer, सहित tobacco उपयोग, निश्चित infections, विकिरण, कमी of शारीरिक कार्यकलाप, obesity, और पर्यावरणीय प्रदूषक.
These can directly damage genes or combine साथ मौजूदा genetic faults भीतर कोशिकाएं to कारण the disease.
Approximately five to टेन प्रतिशत of cancers are entirely hereditary.
कर्कट can be detected in a number of तरीके, सहित the presence of निश्चित signs और symptoms, स्क्रीनिंग tests, or चिकित्सा imaging.
Once a possible कर्कट is detected it is diagnosed by microscopic परिक्षा of a tissue नमूना.
Cancer is usually treated with chemotherapy, radiation therapy और सर्जरी.
the chances of surviving the बीमारी vary greatly by the प्रकार और location of the cancer and the extent of disease at the start of treatment.
जबकि कर्कट can affect people of all आयु, and a few प्रकार of कर्कट are more आम in children, the रिस्क of विकासशील cancer generally increases साथ age.
in 2007, कर्कट caused परिचय 13 % of all इंसान मौतों विश्वव्यापी ( 7.9 million ).
Rates are rising as अधिक लोगों live to an old आयु और as द्रव्यमान lifestyle परिवर्तन occur in the विकासशील संसार.

जॉन मेनार्ड keynes, 1st Baron keynes, cb, FBA ( ; 5 जून 1883 – 21 April 1946 ) was a अंग्रेजों economist जिनकी ideas have fundamentally प्रभावित the सिद्धान्त और practice of आधुनिक macroeconomics, और सूचित the आर्थिक policies of सरकारें.
he निर्मित on और greatly परिष्कृत पहले कार्य on the कल्याणकारी of कारोबार cycles, और is widely considered to be एक of the संस्थापकों of modern macroeconomics और the most influential अर्थशास्त्री of the 20th सदी.
His विचार हैं the आधार for the स्कूल of विचार ज्ञात as keynesian अर्थशास्त्र, as well as its विभिन्न offshoots.
In अनेक तरीके, subsequent developments in 20th century अर्थशास्त्र can be viewed as either building on Keynes ' विचार or reacting विरूद्ध उन्हें.
in the 1930s, keynes पथप्रदर्शन a revolution in आर्थिक सोच, overturning the older विचार of neoclassical अर्थशास्त्र कि held कि free बाज़ार would, in the छोटी to medium term, automatically provide full employment, as long as workers यहूद flexible in their मजदूरी demands.
Keynes बजाय argued कि aggregate माँग संकल्पित the overall level of economic कार्यकलाप, and कि inadequate कुल demand could lead to prolonged periods of high unemployment.
He advocated the उपयोग of fiscal and मौद्रिक उपायों to mitigate the adverse प्रभाव of आर्थिक recessions और depressions.
Following the outbreak of the Second संसार War, keynes 's ideas concerning आर्थिक नीति यहूद adopted by leading पश्चिमी economies.
in 1942, Keynes थी awarded a खानदानी peerage as सामन्त Keynes of Tilton in the County of ससेक्स.
Keynes died in 1946, लकिन दौरान the 1950s और 1960s the success of keynesian अर्थशास्त्र resulted in लगभग सब capitalist सरकारें adopting इसके नीति recommendations.
Keynes 's influence waned in the 1970s, partly as a परिणाम of problems कि began to afflict the anglo-american economies from the प्रारंभ of the दशक, and partly क्युकी of critiques from मिल्टन फ्राइडमैन and other economists who were pessimistic परिचय the क्षमता of governments to विनियमित the business साईकिल with फिस्कल नीति.
however, the advent of the वैश्विक वित्तीय crisis in 2007 caused a पुनरुत्थान in keynesian thought.
Keynesian economics provided the सैद्धांतिक underpinning लिये आर्थिक policies undertaken in जवाब to the संकट by राष्ट्रपतियों George W. Bush और Barack ओबामा of the संयुक्त राज्य, Prime Minister गॉर्डन भूरा of the संयुक्त किंगडम, and अन्य heads of governments.
In 1999, Time magazine included keynes in उनके सूची of the 100 सबसे महत्वपूर्ण और influential लोगों of the 20th सदी, commenting that : `` उसके radical विचार कि सरकारें चाहिए खर्च धन they do n't have may have saved पूंजीवाद. ''
in addition to होने an economist, keynes थी also a civil नौकर, a निदेशक of the अंग्रेजों Eugenics समाज, a निदेशक of the बैंको of England, a संरक्षक of the arts and an art collector, a भाग of the Bloomsbury समूह of intellectuals, an advisor to several charitable trusts, a writer, a पारस, a private निवेशकों, और a किसान.
इस 1768 parchment ( 612×502 mm ) by Jekuthiel sofer emulated the 1675 टेन आयतें at the एम्सटर्डम Esnoga synagogue.
The टेन Commandments, भी ज्ञात as the decalogue, हैं a नियत of biblical कानून relating to ethics और इबादत, जिससे खेल a fundamental भूमिका in judaism, Islam and christianity.
वे शामिल instructions to worship तभी परमेश्वर, to keep the sabbath पावन और prohibitions against idolatry, blasphemy, murder, theft, deception और व्यभिचार.
अलग समूह follow थोड़ा अलग परंपराओं लिये interpreting और क्रमांकन उन्हें.

the डिस्कोग्राफ़ी of the अंग्रेज़ी वैकल्पिक चट्टान बैंड the smiths consists of four studio एल्बम, एक विस्तारित खेल ( EP ), एक live एल्बम, टेन compilation albums, twenty singles, one video एल्बम और चौदह music videos on the अशिष्ट Trade, sire and WEA रिकार्ड लेबल्स.

Gone with the हवा is a अनोखा लिखा by मार्गरेट Mitchell, first प्रकाशित in 1936.
It is प्रायः लगाई in the literary sub-genre of the historical रोमांस novel.
However, it रै महरूम argued the novel is a `` near मिस '' और करता नहीं contain all of the elements of the romance विधा, बनाना it simply a ऐतिहासिक अनोखा.
the story is set in Clayton County, जॉर्जिया, और Atlanta दौरान the अमरीकी सिविल युद्ध and Reconstruction.
It depicts the अनुभवों of Scarlett O'Hara, the बिगड़े बेटी of a well-to-do plantation owner, who जरूर use प्रत्येक means at उसके disposal to come आउट of the गरीबी वो पाता herself in after Sherman 's `` कूच to the Sea ''.
Margaret Mitchell began लिखने गए with the Wind in 1926 to pass the समय while recovering इससे an auto-crash चोट that refused to चंगा.
in April 1935, Harold लैथम of Macmillan, an एडिटर who थी looking for नई fiction, पढ़ा कया she had लिखा और saw कि it could be a best-seller.
बाद लैथम सहमत to publish the book, Mitchell worked लिये another six months checking the ऐतिहासिक references, और rewrote the खोलने chapter अनेक टाइम्स.
Mitchell and her husband John दलदल, a नक़ल editor by व्यापार, संपादित the फाइनल संस्करण of the अनोखा.
मिशेल wrote the किताब 's फाइनल moments पहला, और तब लिखा the कार्यक्रम that led up to it.
As to कया became of her lovers, रहेट और स्कारलेट, बाद the अनोखा ended, Mitchell किया not जान, और said, `` For सब i know, Rhett may have found किसी else जो थी less मुश्किल. ''
मिशेल received the पुलित्जर पुरस्कार लिये fiction लिये the book in 1937.
the किताब थी adapted into a 1939 अमरीकी film.
गए with the हवा is the only novel by Mitchell published दौरान उसके lifetime.
Endodontics ( from the Greek endo `` अंदर '' ; and odons `` tooth '' ) is एक of the दंत specialties पहचाना by the American दंत संघ, royal College of dentists of कनाडा, और royal australasian College of दंत Surgeons, और सौदे with the दाँत pulp and the tissues surrounding the रूट of a दाँत.
Endodontists perform a किस्में of प्रक्रियाओं सहित endodontic चिकित्सा ( commonly ज्ञात as `` रूट canal therapy '' ), endodontic retreatment, सर्जरी, treating cracked teeth, और treating दंत आघात.
Root कनाल therapy is एक of the most आम प्रक्रियाओं.
If the गूदा ( containing nerves, arterioles, venules, lymphatic ऊतक, and fibrous ऊतक ) becomes diseased or घायल, endodontic treatment is required to सहेजें the दाँत.
सीरियल Attached scsi ( SAS ) is a point-to-point serial protocol कि चालें आंकड़ा to और इससे computer भंडार devices such as hard ड्राइव and tape ड्राइव.
SAS replaces the पुरानी समानांतर SCSI ( pronounced `` scuzzy '' ) बस प्रौद्योगिकी कि first appeared in the mid-1980s.
SAS, like इसके पूर्ववर्ती, uses the standard scsi कमांड set.
SAS offers backward संगतता साथ second-generation SATA ड्राइव.
SATA 3 gbit/s ड्राइव may be connected to SAS backplanes, लकिन SAS ड्राइव can नहीं connect to sata backplanes.
the T10 technical कमेटी of the International कमेटी लिये सूचना प्रौद्योगिकी मानकों ( incits ) develops and maintains the sas protocol ; the SCSI व्यापार संघ ( SCSITA ) promotes the प्रौद्योगिकी.

Status as a natural-born नागरिक of the United States is one of the eligibility आवश्यकताएँ स्थापित in the United States संविधान for चुनाव to the दफ्तर of President or Vice अध्यक्ष.
This आवश्यकता थी intended to protect the nation from foreign influence.
the Constitution does not define the phrase natural-born नागरिक, and various राय have been offered over समय regarding its precise meaning.
a 2011 Congressional शोध Service रपट stated
The natural-born-citizen clause रै महरूम उल्लेखित in गुजर in अनेक निर्णय of the संयुक्त राज्य Supreme अदालत और निम्नतर courts dealing साथ the question of पात्रता लिये नागरिकता by birth, but the परम् Court has never सीधे addressed the सवाल of a विशिष्ट अध्यक्षीय or vice-presidential प्रत्याशी 's पात्रता as a natural-born नागरिक.
kurtis Eugene `` Kurt '' warner ( born जून 22, 1971 ) is a former American football खिलाड़ी.
He निभाई quarterback for three National फ़ुटबॉल League ( एनएफएल ) टीमों : the st. Louis Rams, the New यॉर्क दिग्गज, and the एरिज़ोना कार्डिनल्स.
he थी originally हस्ताक्षरित by the ग्रीन खाड़ी पैकर्स as an undrafted फ़्री एजेंट in 1994 बाद playing college फ़ुटबॉल at Northern आयोवा.
warner would go on to be माना the best undrafted खिलाड़ी of all समय, following a 12-year करियर regarded as एक of the महानतम कहानियां in एनएफएल इतिहास.
Warner first attained स्टारडम जबकि playing for the st. लुई Rams इससे 1998 to 2003, where he जीती दो एनएफएल MVP पुरस्कार in 1999 and 2001 as खूब as the सुपर Bowl mvp पुरस्कार in सुपर कटोरी XXXIV.
he led the 2008 एरिज़ोना कार्डिनल्स to सुपर कटोरी XLIII ( the मताधिकार 's पहला Super Bowl berth ), और owns the तीन highest single-game passing yardage totals in सुपर Bowl history.
warner फिलहाल holds the seventh-highest career passer rating of all-time ( 93.7 ), और the third-highest career completion percentage in एनएफएल history with 65.5 %.
in 13 career playoff खेल, warner बाँधने पहला all-time in पूर्णता प्रतिशत ( 66.5 % ), गज per attempt ( 8.55 ), और दूसरी in passer दरजा ( 102.8 ).
He भी holds the highest completion प्रतिशत लिये a सिंगल खेल दौरान the नियमित season, at 92.3 प्रतिशत ( 24/26 ), on सितंबर 20, 2009, विरूद्ध the Jacksonville Jaguars.
He घोषित उसके retirement on January 29, 2010. < संदर्भ name='cnn 2010-01-29 ' >
जेनेट Kay ruthven hagan ( ; born May 26, 1953 ) is the जूनियर United राज्य Senator इससे North कैरोलिना, in office चूंकि जनवरी 2009.
previously she परोसा in the North कैरोलिना Senate इससे 1999 to 2009.

जब hagan पराजित रिपब्लिकन incumbent एलिज़ाबेथ Dole in the 2008 संयुक्त राज्य Senate election, वो became the पहला woman to शिकस्त an लाज़िम स्त्री in a सीनेट चुनाव.
the heisman मेमोरियल Trophy पुरस्कार ( प्रायः known colloquially as the heisman ट्रॉफी or the Heisman ), is awarded annually to the खिलाड़ी deemed the सबसे बकाया खिलाड़ी in कॉलेजिएट फ़ुटबॉल.
it थी निर्मित in 1935 as the Downtown एथलेटिक Club ट्रॉफी and renamed in 1936 following the मौत of the Club 's athletic director, John heisman ( former भूरा विश्वविद्यालयों और विश्वविद्यालयों of Pennsylvania player ; सिर फ़ुटबॉल कोच at oberlin कॉलेज, auburn विश्वविद्यालयों, clemson University, Rice विश्वविद्यालयों, और the विश्वविद्यालयों of Pennsylvania ; और फ़ुटबॉल, बास्केट, and बेसबॉल head coach और athletic निदेशक at Georgia तकनीक ).
the पुरस्कार is प्रस्तुत by the heisman Trophy विश्वास in early December before the postseason bowl खेल.
it is the oldest of अनेक overall awards in college फ़ुटबॉल, सहित the मैक्सवेल पुरस्कार, वाल्टर Camp पुरस्कार, और the ap Player of the Year.
the heisman and the ap खिलाड़ी of the साल are the तभी पुरस्कार to honor the most बकाया खिलाड़ी, while the Maxwell पुरस्कार और वाल्टर शिविर Award recognize the बेहतरीन खिलाड़ी, और the आर्ची griffin पुरस्कार recognizes the सबसे मूल्यवान player.
The United राष्ट्र कमांड ( unc ) is the एकीकृत कमांड ढांचा लिये the multinational सैन्य शक्तियां supporting the गणतंत्र of कोरियाई ( दक्षिण कोरियाई or ROK ) during and बाद the कोरियाई युद्ध.
बाद troops of the लोकतांत्रिक लोगों 's Republic of कोरियाई ( North कोरियाई or dprk ) invaded दक्षिण कोरियाई on June 25, 1950, the संयुक्त राष्ट्र Security परिषद adopted Resolution 82 calling on उत्तर कोरियाई to cease hostilities and withdraw to the 38th parallel.
on जून 27, 1950, it अपनाया Resolution 83, recommending कि members of the United राष्ट्र provide सहायता to the गणतंत्र of Korea `` to repel the हथियारबंद attack और to restore अंतरराष्ट्रीय सलाम और security to the area ''.
सुरक्षा Council रेज़ोल्यूशन 84, अपनाया on जुलाई 7, 1950, recommended कि members providing military forces and other सहायता to दक्षिण Korea `` make ऐसे forces and other assistance उपलब्धियाँ to a एकीकृत कमांड अंतर्गत the संयुक्त राज्य of अमेरिका ''.
Although the resolutions सुझाया the forces under the unc were `` संयुक्त राष्ट्र शक्तियां '', और संयुक्त Nations itself could be माना a belligerent, in practice the संयुक्त राष्ट्र exercised no कंट्रोल over the कॉम्बैट शक्तियां, जिससे यहूद controlled by the संयुक्त राज्य.
Most observers concluded कि the शक्तियां अंतर्गत the unc यहूद नहीं in विधि संयुक्त राष्ट्र सैनिकों, and the acts of the UNC were not the अधिनियमों of the संयुक्त Nations.
the UNC can be regarded as an गठबंधन of नेशनल सेना, operating under the सामूहिक सही of self-defense.
On अगस्त 29, 1950, the अंग्रेजों Commonwealth 's 27th infantry Brigade arrived at Busan to जुड़ें the UNC, which जबतक तब शामिल तभी ROK और u.S. शक्तियां.
The 27th ब्रिगेड moved into the naktong नदी line वेस्ट of daegu.
troop इकाई from अन्य countries of the un followed in rapid succession ; Australia, belgian United राष्ट्र कमांड, Canada, कोलंबिया, इथियोपिया, France, Greece, Luxembourg, the नीदरलैंड्स, नई जीलैंड, the फिलीपीन, थाईलैंड और Turkey.
the Union of दक्षिण Africa provided एयर इकाई जिससे लड़ा alongside the एयर शक्तियां of other member राष्ट्र.
Denmark, इण्डिया, नार्वे, and स्वीडन provided चिकित्सा इकाई.
Italy provided a हॉस्पिटल, भी हालांकि it थी not a un सदस्य.
the संयुक्त Nations कमांड और the chinese-north Korean Command हस्ताक्षरित the Korean armistice अनुबंध on 27 जुलाई 1953, ending the भारी लड़.
The armistice अनुबंध established the Military armistice Commission ( मैक ), consisting of representatives of the two signatories, to supervise the क्रियान्वयन of the armistice शर्तें.
The North Korean-Chinese मैक रै महरूम replaced by panmumjon प्रतिनिधि under exclusive उत्तर कोरियाई प्रबन्धन.

lincoln हाइट्स is an American परिवार drama television series परिचय एडी Sutton, a मिशन विस्टा पुलिस अधिकारी who चालें उसके family back to his बूढ़ा पड़ोस, lincoln हाइट्स, to start a नई life and to help आउट उसके old पड़ोस.

A ईसाई denomination is an identifiable धार्मिक देह under a common नाम, ढांचा, और doctrine भीतर Christianity.
in the Orthodox परंपरा, churches हैं विभाजित प्रायः along जातीय and भाषाई lines, into separate चर्च और traditions.
Technically, विभाजन between एक group और another हैं defined by doctrine and church authority.
मुद्दे ऐसे as the प्रकृति of Jesus, the प्राधिकार of अपोस्टोलिक succession, eschatology, and papal primacy पृथक एक denomination from another.
the रोमन Catholic Church is the largest denomination साथ over 1.1 अरब members, over हाफ of all ईसाइयों worldwide, making it the largest denomination for कोई धर्म विश्वव्यापी ( हालांकि the गिरिजाघर does not दृश्य itself as a denomination, लकिन as the original pre-denominational church ).
प्रोटोस्टेंट denominations comprise roughly 38–39 % of ईसाइयों विश्वव्यापी, और साथ the catholics, Protestants, anglicans, और अन्य closely related denominations comprise Western christianity.
The Eastern Orthodox गिरिजाघर, Oriental Orthodox Churches और the assyrian गिरिजाघर of the East हैं माना Eastern Christian denominations.
Western Christian denominations prevail in पश्चिमी यूरोपीय and इसके पूर्व colonies.
पूर्वी ईसाई denominations are represented mostly in पूर्वी Europe, the मध्य East and North Africa.
ईसाइयों have विभिन्न doctrines परिचय the गिरिजाघर, the body of faithful कि वे मानना थी स्थापित by यीशु Christ, और कैसा the दैवी church corresponds to ईसाई denominations.
दोनो the Catholics और the पूर्वी परंपरागत consider प्रत्येक of themselves solely to faithfully represent the एक पावन कैथोलिक और अपोस्टोलिक Church to the exclusion of the अन्य.
Protestants separated इससे the कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर क्युकी of theologies और practices कि they considered to be in उल्लंघन of उनके interpretation.
generally, members of the various denominations acknowledge प्रत्येक अन्य as Christians, at least to the extent that they have mutually पहचाना baptisms और acknowledge historically परंपरागत views सहित the देवत्व of यीशु और doctrines of सिन and मोक्ष, भी हालांकि doctrinal and ecclesiological obstacles hinder full नियाज़ between चर्च.
चूंकि the reforms surrounding वेटिकन ii, the Catholic गिरिजाघर has referred to Protestant समुदायों as `` denominations '', जबकि reserving the पद `` गिरिजाघर '' for अपोस्टोलिक churches, सहित the Eastern परंपरागत ( देखिए subsistit in और branch theory ).
There हैं however some non-denominational Christians जो do नहीं follow कोई particular शाखा.
the पांडा ( ailuropoda melanoleuca, lit.
`` black और श्वेत cat-foot '' ), also ज्ञात as the दानव panda to फर्क it from the unrelated red पांडा, is a भालू native to central-western और दक्षिण western चीन.
it is easily पहचाना by the विशाल, distinctive ब्लैक धब्बे around इसके eyes, over the कानों, और across its गोलाकार body.
Though it belongs to the अनुक्रम carnivora, the panda 's आहार is 99 % बाँसुरी.
Pandas in the wild will occasionally eat अन्य grasses, जंगली tubers, or भी मांस in the रूप of पक्षियों, rodents or carrion.
in captivity, वे may प्राप्त मधु, अंडे, मछली, yams, shrub पत्ते, संतरे, or bananas along साथ विशेषकर prepared food.
the दानव panda जीवनदान in a few mountain सीमाएँ in central China, mainly in Sichuan province, but भी in the shaanxi and गांसू provinces.
as a परिणाम of farming, deforestation और other development, the panda has been चलित आउट of the lowland क्षेत्रों जहाँ it एकबार lived.
the panda is a संरक्षण reliant endangered प्रजाति.
A 2007 रपट shows 239 pandas living in captivity inside चीन and another 27 outside the देश.
जंगली population estimates vary ; one estimate shows that वहीँ हैं about 1,590 individuals living in the जंगली, जबकि a 2006 study via डीएनए analysis अनुमानित कि this figure could be as ऊँची as 2,000 to 3,000.
कुछ reports भी दिखाएँ that the क्रमांक of pandas in the जंगली is on the वृद्धि.
However, the आईयूसीएन करता नहीं believe वहीँ is enough certainty yet to reclassify the प्रजाति इससे endangered to vulnerable.
जबकि the ड्रैगन रै often परोसा as China 's national emblem, internationally the पांडा appears at तनिक as commonly.
as ऐसे, it is becoming widely प्रयुक्त भीतर China in international contexts, लिये example the five Fuwa mascots of the Beijing ओलंपिक.
the Kite धावक is a 2007 अमरीकी नाटक फिल्मी निर्देशित by मार्क Forster based on the novel of the वही name by Khaled Hosseini.

The स्टोरी is set विरूद्ध a backdrop of उग्र कार्यक्रम, from the fall of the monarchy in अफगानिस्तान through the Soviet सैन्य intervention, the द्रव्यमान exodus of Afghan शरणार्थियों to पाकिस्तानी and the संयुक्त States, and the तालिबान शासन.

the legality of कैनबिस varies इससे देश to देश.
Possession of cannabis is illegal in most countries and has been चूंकि the शुरूआत of widespread कैनबिस निषेध in the लेट 1930s.
however, अनेक देशों have decriminalized the कब्ज़ा of small quantities of कैनबिस, particularly in North अमेरिका, South अमेरिका and Europe.
furthermore, possession is विधिक or effectively विधिक in the Netherlands, North कोरियाई and would be in the u.S. राज्य of कोलोराडो and वॉशिंगटन if it were not लिये federal विधि, जिससे governs व्यक्तियों in all राज्य.
the medicinal उपयोग of cannabis is विधिक in a क्रमांक of देशों, including कनाडा, the चेक Republic और इसराईल.
While संघीय विधि in the संयुक्त राज्य bans सब sale और possession of कैनबिस, प्रवर्तन varies widely at the राज्य level और कुछ राज्य have established औषधीय मारिजुआना programs in that contradict संघीय विधि ; दो राज्य ( Colorado and वॉशिंगटन ) have repealed their कानून prohibiting the recreational उपयोग of कैनबिस and replaced उन्हें साथ a regulatory regime, also contrary to federal statute.
कुछ देशों have laws कि हैं not as vigorously prosecuted as अन्य लकिन, apart इससे the countries that प्रस्ताव अभिगम to चिकित्सा मारिजुआना, most countries have various दंड ranging इससे lenient to बहुत कठोर.
Some infractions हैं लिया more seriously in कुछ देशों than others in लिहाज़ to the cultivation, उपयोग, कब्ज़ा or ट्रांसफ़र of cannabis लिये recreational use.
A few jurisdictions have lessened दंड लिये कब्ज़ा of small quantities of कैनबिस, making it दंडनीय by confiscation और a ठीक, बल्कि than कारावास.
Some क्षेत्राधिकारs/ ड्रग courts उपयोग अनिवार्य treatment कार्यक्रम लिये young or बारंबार उपयोक्ता, साथ स्वतंत्रता इससे narcotic दवाएँ as the लक्ष्य and a few jurisdictions परमिट कैनबिस उपयोग for औषधीय purposes.
वहीँ are भी changes in a अधिक restrictive दिशा as in कनाडा.
ड्रग परीक्षण to detect कैनबिस are increasingly आम in many countries और have resulted in jail वाक्य और लोगों खोने their कार्य.
However, सरल possession can carry long jail वाक्य in कुछ देशों, विशेषकर in भाग of ईस्ट Asia and southeast एशिया where the बिक्री of कैनबिस may सीसे to a sentence of life in थाना or भी निष्पादन.

epithelium is एक of the चार मौलिक types of एनिमल ऊतक, साथ with संयोजी ऊतक, muscle tissue और nervous tissue.

Functions of epithelial कोशिकाएं include स्राव, selective अवशोषण, protection, transcellular transport और detection of सनसनी.
In यूनानी `` ἐπί '' ( `` epi '' ) अर्थात् `` on '' or `` upon '', और `` θηλή '' ( `` thēlē '' ) means `` nipple ''.

the comanche हैं a मैदान भारतीय जनजाति जिनकी historic territory, ज्ञात as Comancheria, consisted of उपस्थित day eastern नई मैक्सिको, दक्षिणी Colorado, northeastern एरिज़ोना, दक्षिणी कान्सास, सब of ओक्लाहोमा, और सबसे of northwest टेक्सास.

historically, the Comanches were hunter-gatherers with a घोड़ा संस्कृति.
वहीँ may have महरूम as many as 45,000 Comanches in the लेट 18th century.
आज, the Comanche स्वदेश comanche tribal नामांकन numbers 15,191 साथ approximately 7,763 members residing in the lawton – फोर्ट sill and surrounding areas of दक्षिणपश्चिम ओक्लाहोमा.
the comanche स्वदेश Homecoming powwow is आयोजित annually in Walters, Oklahoma in mid-july.
the comanche spoke the Comanche language, a Numic language of the uto-aztecan परिवार, sometimes classified as a Shoshone dialect ; however, तभी परिचय 1 % of Comanches speak it आज.

Coca-Cola is a कार्बोनेटेड नरम पेय बेची in स्टोर्स, restaurants, और vending मशीने in प्रत्येक देश except क्यूबा और उत्तर कोरियाई.
it is उत्पादित by the Coca-Cola कम्पनी of Atlanta, Georgia, and is often referred to बस as Coke ( a registered ट्रेडमार्क of the Coca-Cola कम्पनी in the संयुक्त राज्य since कूच 27, 1944 ).
originally intended as a patent आयुर्विज्ञान when it थी invented in the late 19th century by जॉन pemberton, coca-cola थी खरीदा out by बिजनेसमैन asa griggs candler, जिनकी विपणन tactics led कोक to its दबदबा of the world soft-drink मार्केट throughout the 20th सदी.
The कम्पनी produces concentrate, which is तब sold to licensed Coca-Cola bottlers throughout the संसार.
the bottlers, जो थाम territorially विशेष अनुबंध साथ the कम्पनी, produce finished product in cans and bottles from the concentrate in संयोजन with filtered जल and sweeteners.
the bottlers तब बेचें, वितरित and merchandise Coca-Cola to खुदरा स्टोर्स और वेंडिंग मशीने.
ऐसे bottlers शामिल coca-cola उद्यमों, जिससे is the largest सिंगल Coca-Cola bottler in North अमेरिका and पश्चिमी Europe.
the coca-cola कम्पनी also बिकता concentrate for soda स्रोतों to प्रमुख रेस्तरां और खाना service distributors.
the coca-cola कम्पनी रै, on occasion, introduced अन्य cola drinks अंतर्गत the Coke brand नाम.
The सबसे आम of ये is आहार कोक, साथ अन्य सहित Caffeine-Free Coca-Cola, Diet कोक caffeine-free, coca-cola Cherry, coca-cola Zero, coca-cola Vanilla, और खास संस्करण साथ नीबू, लाइम or coffee.

प्रकार of bar-lines
in musical संकेतन, a बार ( or माप ) is a खण्ड of समय पारिभाषित by a दिए क्रमांक of बीट्स, each of which are आबंटित a particular नोट value.
dividing म्यूज़िक into bars provides नियमित reference points to pin point locations भीतर a टुकड़ा of music.
it also makes written music easier to follow, since प्रत्येक बार of स्टाफ प्रतीकों can be पढ़ा और निभाई as a batch.
Typically, a piece consists of several बार of the वही length, और in आधुनिक musical संकेतन the क्रमांक of बीट्स in each bar is specified at the beginning of the score by the top number of a time हस्ताक्षर ( such as 3/4 ), while the नीचे क्रमांक indicates the नोट मान of the ताल ( the beat रै a quarter नोट मान in the 3/4 example ).
the शब्द बार is more common in British English, and the word माप is more आम in American अंग्रेज़ी, हालांकि संगीतकारों generally understand both usages.
in अमरीकी अंग्रेज़ी, although the शब्द बार and माप हैं often used interchangeably the सही उपयोग of the शब्द 'bar ' refers तभी to the लंबवत line itself, जबकि the शब्द 'measure ' refers to the बीट्स contained between bars.
In अंतरराष्ट्रीय उपयोग, it is equally सही to speak of बार संख्याएँ and measure संख्याएँ, e.g. ‘bars 9–16’ or ‘mm. 9–16’.
Along the वही लाइनों, it is हिकमत to आरक्षित the abbreviated रूप ‘bb.
3–4’ etc. लिये beats तभी ; बार चाहिए be referred to by नाम in full.
The first metrically पूरा माप within a टुकड़ा of music is पुकारा ‘bar 1’ or ‘m. 1’.
जब the टुकड़ा begins with an anacrusis ( an incomplete measure at the head of a piece of म्यूज़िक ), ‘bar 1’ or ‘m. 1’ is the following माप.
The 19.9 MW gemasolar सौर plant in स्पेन features 15 घंटों of भंडार and can supply शक्ति 24 hours a दिन.
Solar energy, रौशन light और heat from the सूर्य, has महरूम harnessed by humans चूंकि ancient times using a दायरा of ever-evolving technologies.
सौर उर्जा technologies शामिल सौर हीटिंग, solar photovoltaics, सौर thermal electricity, solar architecture and कृत्रिम photosynthesis, which can मेक considerable योगदान to solving some of the most urgent उर्जा problems the संसार अभी चेहरों.
सौर technologies हैं broadly characterized as either passive सौर or क्रियाशील सौर depending on the रास्ता वे कैप्चर, convert और distribute सौर energy.
क्रियाशील सौर तकनीकों शामिल the use of photovoltaic panels और सौर thermal collectors to harness the उर्जा.
Passive सौर तकनीकों include orienting a भवन to the सूर्य, selecting materials साथ favorable थर्मल mass or लाइट dispersing properties, and डिजाइनिंग स्पेसेस कि naturally circulate air.
in 2011, the अंतरराष्ट्रीय उर्जा एजेंसी said that `` the विकास of affordable, inexhaustible और साफ सौर energy technologies होगा have विशाल longer-term लाभ.
It will बढ़ाएँ countries’ energy सुरक्षा through रिलायंस on an स्वदेशी, inexhaustible और mostly import-independent संसाधन, बढ़ाएँ sustainability, reduce pollution, निम्नतर the लागत of mitigating जलवायु बदलें, और रखना चट्टान fuel कीमतें lower than otherwise.
ये लाभ are global.
Hence the additional लागत of the प्रोत्साहन for जल्दी deployment चाहिए be considered learning investments ; they जरूर be बुद्धिमानी खर्च और need to be widely shared ''.
प्राथमिक परवाह may be provided in जातियाँ स्वास्थ्य केंद्रों.
प्राथमिक care is the स्वास्थ्य परवाह दिए by a स्वास्थ्य परवाह प्रदाता.
typically this प्रदाता अधिनियमों as the principal पाइंट of परामर्श लिये patients within a स्वास्थ्य परवाह system और निर्देशांक अन्य specialists कि the रोगी may need.
Such a professional can be a प्राथमिक परवाह चिकित्सक, ऐसे as a general practitioner or family physician, or depending on the मोहल्ले, स्वास्थ्य प्रणाली संगठन, और patient 's discretion, वे may see a फार्मासिस्ट, a physician assistant, a नर्स practitioner, a nurse ( such as in the United किंगडम ), a नैदानिक अधिकारी ( ऐसे as in parts of Africa ), or an आयुर्वेदिक or अन्य traditional आयुर्विज्ञान पेशेवर ( ऐसे as in भाग of एशिया ).
Depending on the प्रकृति of the health कंडीशन, patients may तब be referred लिये secondary or tertiary परवाह.

psychiatrists are प्राधिकृत to prescribe आयुर्विज्ञान, conduct शारीरिक examinations, order and interpret प्रयोगशाला परीक्षण, use मनोचिकित्सा और may अनुक्रम brain imaging अध्ययन such as computed tomography ( CT/CAT Scan ), चुम्बकीय resonance imaging ( mri ), and positron उत्सर्जन टोमोग्राफी ( पालतु ) स्कैनिंग.
Within the फ्रेमवर्क of the World Health संगठन 's ( जो ) definition of स्वास्थ्य as a state of complete physical, दिमागी और सोशल well-being, and नहीं merely the अनुपस्थिति of बीमारी or infirmity, reproductive स्वास्थ्य, or sexual health/hygiene, addresses the reproductive प्रक्रियाओं, कृत्यों and system at सब चरण of life.
Reproductive स्वास्थ्य, therefore, implies that people are able to have a जिम्मेदार, संतोषजनक और safer sex जीवन और कि they have the काबिलियत to reproduce and the स्वतंत्रता to decide if, जब and how प्रायः to do so.
एक निर्वचन of इस implies that मेन और महिलाओं ought to be informed of and to have अभिगम to सुरक्षित, प्रभावी, affordable और स्वीकार्य विधि of जनम control ; also access to appropriate स्वास्थ्य परवाह सेवाएं of sexual, reproductive medicine और implementation of स्वास्थ्य शिक्षा कार्यक्रम to तनाव the महत्व of women to go सकुशल through गर्भावस्था और प्रसव could provide युगल साथ the बेहतरीन chance of having a स्वस्थ शिशु.
on the other hand individuals do फेस inequalities in reproductive स्वास्थ्य सेवाएं.
inequalities vary आधारित on socioeconomic औकात, शिक्षा level, आयु, नस्ल, धर्म, and संसाधन available in उनके environment.
It is संभावित लिये example, कि कम आय individuals कमी the संसाधन लिये appropriate स्वास्थ्य सेवाएं and the ज्ञान to जान what is उचित लिये maintaining reproductive health.
according to the जो, `` Reproductive and sexual ill-health accounts लिये 20 % of the वैश्विक बोझ of ill-health for महिलाओं, and 14 % for men. ''
reproductive स्वास्थ्य is a भाग of यौन और reproductive health और rights.

कोर 2 is a ब्रांड encompassing a दायरा of इंटेल 's उपभोक्ता 64-bit x86-64 single-, दुआl-, और quad-core microprocessors आधारित on the कोर microarchitecture.
The single- और dual-core models हैं single- die, whereas the quad-core models comprise दो dies, प्रत्येक containing दो cores, packaged in a multi-chip मोड्यूल.
The परिचय of Core 2 relegated the pentium brand to the mid-range market, और reunified लैपटॉप और desktop cpu लाइनों, which previously था महरूम विभाजित into the Pentium 4, pentium d, and pentium M ब्रांड्स.

the सुपर कटोरी is the annual चैंपियनशिप खेल of the नेशनल फ़ुटबॉल लीग ( एनएफएल ), the उच्चतम स्तर of पेशेवर American फ़ुटबॉल in the United राज्य, culminating a season कि begins in the लेट summer of the previous calendar साल.
the सुपर कटोरी उपयोग Roman numerals to identify प्रत्येक खेल, बल्कि than the साल in जिससे it is held.
लिये example, सुपर Bowl I थी played on जनवरी 15, 1967, following the 1966 नियमित ऋतु, जबकि सुपर Bowl xlvii थी निभाई on फ़रवरी 3, 2013, following the 2012 ऋतु.
the game was निर्मित as भाग of a विलय अनुबंध between the एनएफएल और its then-rival league, the American Football लीग ( afl ).

बाद the विलय, each लीग थी redesignated as a `` सम्मेलन ``, and the खेल थी then निभाई between the सम्मेलन champions.
Currently, the National Football सम्मेलन ( NFC ) लीड the श्रेणी साथ 25 विन्स to 22 विन्स for the अमरीकी फ़ुटबॉल सम्मेलन ( afc ).
the day on जिससे the सुपर कटोरी is निभाई, अभी considered by कुछ a de facto American नेशनल holiday, is called `` सुपर Bowl Sunday ``.
it is the second-largest day लिये u.S. food खपत, बाद थैंक्सगिविंग Day.
In जोड, the Super Bowl has frequently महरूम the सबसे watched अमरीकी television broadcast of the साल.

क्युकी of its ऊँची viewership, commercial airtime during the सुपर कटोरी broadcast is the most expensive of the year.
due to the ऊँची cost of निवेश in advertising on the सुपर कटोरी, कंपनियाँ regularly develop उनके सबसे expensive advertisements लिये this ब्रॉडकास्ट.

फिओना is a feminine दिए नाम.
The name फिओना was invented, and पहला used, by the स्कॉटिश poet James macpherson ( 1736–96 ), author of the Ossian poems, जिससे he claimed were अनुवाद from प्राचीन गैलिक स्त्रोत ( स्त्रोत, जब challenged, he never produced ).
The name थी subsequently प्रयुक्त as a pseudonym by William Sharp ( 1855–1905 ), who authored अनेक romantic works अंतर्गत the नाम `` फिओना Macleod ''.
the name रै चूंकि become popular in इंग्लैण्ड, स्कॉटलैंड and आयरलैंड.
the नाम is माना to be a latinised रूप of the Gaelic शब्द fionn, अर्थ `` श्वेत '', `` मेला ''.
the name फिओना is भी sometimes used as an Anglicisation of the irish-language name fíona, हालांकि ये names are otherwise unrelated ( as fíona is निकला इससे an तत्व अर्थ `` बेल '' ).
There is also a आधुनिक tendency to equate the प्रामाणिक Scottish Gaelic feminine name fionnghal साथ Fiona.
the name Fiona is उठती in लोकप्रियता particularly in जर्मनी -speaking countries.
फिओना थी the 49th सबसे popular नाम लिये baby लड़कियों born in 2008 in Germany.
Fiona थी tied लिये third प्लेस in the ranking of most लोकप्रिय names लिये baby girls born in the tiny principality of Liechtenstein in 2008.
the नाम was the 347th सबसे लोकप्रिय नाम for लड़कियों born in the संयुक्त States in 2008, जहाँ it has क्रमित among the top 1,000 सबसे popular names लिये girls since 1990 और among the शीर्ष 500 चूंकि 1999.
The नाम फिओना has महरूम विशेषकर लोकप्रिय लिये girls of एशियाई or Pacific Islander descent in New यॉर्क City, where Fiona क्रमित as the ninth most लोकप्रिय नाम लिये लड़कियों इससे those समूह in 2007.
Many भाषाएं हैं used, or historically have महरूम used in the United राज्य.
The most commonly used भाषा is English.
वहीँ are also अनेक languages स्वदेशी to उत्तर America or to U.S. राज्य or holdings in the प्रशांत प्रदेश.
भाषाएं brought to the देश by colonists or immigrants from Europe, Asia, or other भाग of the world मेक up a large portion of the भाषाएं फिलहाल प्रयुक्त ; several languages, including creoles और sign भाषाएं, have भी विकसित in the संयुक्त राज्य.
लगभग 337 भाषाएं हैं बोला or signed by the जनसांख्यिकी, of जिससे 176 are indigenous to the क्षेत्रफल.
Fifty-two languages formerly बोला in the देश 's territory are now विलुप्त.
The किस्में of English spoken in the संयुक्त राज्य is known as अमरीकी English.
अंग्रेज़ी is the de facto नेशनल भाषा of the संयुक्त राज्य, साथ 80 % of the population claiming it as a माँ tongue, and कुछ 95 % claiming to बोलो it `` खूब '' or `` बहुत खूब ''.
however, no official भाषा exists at the संघीय स्तर.
वहीँ have been अनेक proposals to मेक English the national भाषा in amendments to आव्रजन सुधार bills, but none of ये बिल्स रै become विधि with the amendment intact.
the हालात is quite varied at the राज्य और territorial levels, with some राज्य mirroring the संघीय policy of adopting no आधिकारिक language in a de jure capacity, अन्य adopting English अलोन, अन्य officially adopting अंग्रेज़ी as खूब as local भाषाएं, और still अन्य adopting a नीति of de facto bilingualism.
स्पेनी is the दूसरी most common भाषा in the देश, and is spoken by over 12 % of the population.
The United States holds the world 's पांचवां largest spanish-speaking population, outnumbered only by मैक्सिको, स्पेन, कोलंबिया, और अर्जेंटीना.
Throughout the southwestern United राज्य, long-established spanish-speaking समुदायों coexist साथ large संख्याएँ of more हाल hispanophone immigrants.
हालांकि many नई लैटिन अमरीकी immigrants are less than fluent in अंग्रेज़ी, nearly all second-generation Hispanic अमेरिकी बोलो अंग्रेज़ी धड़ल्ले, जबकि only about हाफ स्टिल बोलो Spanish.
according to the 2000 us जनसांख्यिकी, लोगों of जर्मनी ancestry मेक up the largest सिंगल जातीय समूह in the संयुक्त राज्य, और the जर्मनी भाषा ranks fifth.
इतालवी, Polish, and फ्रेंच हैं स्टिल widely बोला among populations descending इससे आप्रवासियों इससे those countries in the जल्दी 20th सदी, but the उपयोग of ये भाषाएं is dwindling as the पुरानी पीढियां die.
रूसी is also spoken by immigrant populations.
Tagalog and वियतनामी have over एक लाख अध्यक्षों प्रत्येक in the United States, almost entirely within हाल immigrant populations.
दोनो भाषाएं, साथ साथ the varieties of the Chinese भाषा, Japanese, and कोरियाई, are अभी used in चुनावों in अलास्का, California, हवाई, Illinois, नई यॉर्क, टेक्सास, and Washington.
देशी अमरीकी languages हैं बोला in smaller pockets of the country, but these populations हैं अवरोहण, और the भाषाएं हैं लगभग never widely used बाहर of reservations.
हवाई, although having few देशी अध्यक्षों, is an official भाषा along साथ अंग्रेज़ी at the state स्तर in हवाई.
The राज्य सरकारी of louisiana offers सेवाएं और documents in फ्रेंच, as करता नई मैक्सिको in Spanish.

1990 's pontiac Grand am सेडान फेंडर और quarter फलक
On an ऑटोमोबाइल, a क्वार्टर panel ( or rear wing as it is known in अंग्रेजों English ) is usually considered the body फलक which goes between the पश्च door और the ट्रंक and typically wraps around the wheel खूब ; however, the similar front section फेंडर ( vehicle ), between the द्वार और the हुड, is sometimes incorrectly referred to as a क्वार्टर फलक.
the क्वार्टर panel is typically बना of Sheet मेटल, लकिन is sometimes बना of fiberglass or fiber-reinforced प्लास्टिक ; हालांकि, इस varies साथ different makes और मॉडल.
a quarter panel is typically a welded on घटक of the uni-body ढांचा or Monocoque.
बदलना of a चादर metal क्वार्टर फलक typically requires it to be काटें off the गाडी and a बदलना भाग to be welded ( or sometimes बंधुआ ) to the गाडी.

shropshire ( or ; alternatively salop ; abbreviated, in print only, shrops ) is a county in the वेस्ट Midlands region of England.
it सीमायें वेल्स to the वेस्ट, चेशायर to the उत्तर, staffordshire to the east, Worcestershire to the south-east and herefordshire to the दक्षिण.
a एकात्मक प्राधिकार ( Shropshire परिषद ) was निर्मित on 1 April 2009, taking over इससे the previous county council and 5 district councils, और कवर most of the काउंटी.
the borough of telford और Wrekin has been a पृथक एकात्मक authority चूंकि 1998 लकिन continues to be शामिल in the ceremonial काउंटी.
The county 's population और economy is centred on पाँच कस्बों : the काउंटी town of Shrewsbury, जिससे is culturally और historically important and is स्तिथ in the केन्द्र of the काउंटी ; telford, a new कस्बा in the east जिससे थी constructed around a क्रमांक of पुरानी towns, सबसे notably Wellington, dawley और Madeley, जिससे is आज the most populous ; and Oswestry in the north-west, Bridgnorth just to the दक्षिण of telford, और Ludlow in the south.
the काउंटी has अनेक further मार्केट कस्बों, सहित whitchurch in the उत्तर, न्यूपोर्ट just to the north-east of telford, और मार्केट drayton in the north-east of the काउंटी.
The Ironbridge Gorge area is a युनेस्को संसार Heritage साईट, covering Ironbridge, coalbrookdale और a part of madeley.
वहीँ हैं, additionally, अन्य notable ऐतिहासिक industrial sites located around the county, ऐसे as at shrewsbury, Broseley, Snailbeach और highley as well as the Shropshire Union कनाल.
the Shropshire पहाड़ियाँ क्षेत्रफल of बकाया प्राकृतिक सौंदर्य covers परिचय a क्वार्टर of the काउंटी, मुख्यतः in the south.
Shropshire is one of इंग्लैण्ड 's सबसे ग्रामीण और sparsely आबादी counties, साथ the population घनत्व of the Shropshire परिषद area होने बस 91/km2 ( 337/sq mi ).
the Wrekin is एक of the सबसे famous प्राकृतिक लैंडमार्क in the काउंटी, हालांकि the उच्चतम पहाड़ियाँ हैं the clee Hills, Stiperstones और the Long Mynd.
Wenlock किनारे is another significant geographical and geological लैंडमार्क.
In the low-lying उत्तरपश्चिम of the county ( और अतिव्यापी the border साथ वेल्स ) is the fenn 's, whixall और Bettisfield mosses नेशनल Nature आरक्षित, one of the most महत्वपूर्ण and बेहतरीन preserved bogs in ब्रिटेन.
The नदी Severn, ग्रेट Britain 's longest river, रनों through the county, exiting into Worcestershire via the severn घाटी.
shropshire is landlocked, और साथ an area of, is England 's largest अंतर्देशीय county.
The काउंटी flower is the round-leaved sundew.
लिये eurostat उद्देश्य, the काउंटी ( कम the एकात्मक ज़िला of telford and Wrekin ) is a NUTS 3 प्रदेश ( code UKG22 ).
the दो shropshire एकात्मक areas ( covering सब of the ceremonial काउंटी ), together साथ the अधिकारियों covering the ceremonial काउंटी of staffordshire, comprise the `` Shropshire और Staffordshire '' NUTS 2 region.

वाट phra kaew, बैंकॉक, थाईलैंड

According to the पिछला census ( 2000 ) 94.6 % of thais are Buddhists of the थेरवाद tradition.
मुसलमान हैं the दूसरी largest religious समूह in थाईलैंड at 4.6 %.
थाईलैंड 's southernmost प्रांतों - pattani, yala, narathiwat and part of songkhla chumphon have dominant मुस्लिम populations, consisting of दोनो जातीय Thai और मलय.
The दक्षिणी टिप of Thailand is ज़्यादातर ethnic Malays.
ईसाइयों, मुख्यतः catholics, represent 0.7 % of the जनसांख्यिकी.
A small लकिन influential जातियाँ of सिखों in Thailand and कुछ Hindus भी सजीव in the country 's cities, and हैं heavily सगाई in खुदरा कॉमर्स.

A value added कर ( vat ) is a रूप of खपत कर.
इससे the परिप्रेक्ष्य of the खरीदार, it is a कर on the purchase price.
इससे कि of the विक्रेता, it is a कर only on the value added to a उत्पाद, सामग्री, or service, from an हिसाब पाइंट of view, by इस stage of its manufacture or वितरण.
The निर्माता remits to the सरकारी the difference between ये दो amounts, and retains the बाकी लिये themselves to ऑफसेट the taxes they had previously सशुल्क on the inputs.
the मान added to a product by or साथ a कारोबार is the बिक्री दाम चार्ज to इसके customer, ऋण the लागत of materials और अन्य taxable inputs.
A vat is जैसे a बिक्री कर in कि ultimately only the समाप्त उपभोक्ता is taxed.
it differs इससे the sales कर in that, with the latter, the tax is collected और remitted to the सरकारी only once, at the पाइंट of खरीदें by the end consumer.
With the vat, collections, remittances to the सरकारी, and क्रेडिट लिये कर already सशुल्क occur प्रत्येक समय a business in the supply कड़ी purchases उत्पाद.
a referee कॉलिंग a high-sticking penaltyHigh
-sticking is the name of दो infractions in the खेल of ice हॉकी कि may occur when a खिलाड़ी intentionally or inadvertently plays साथ उसके or उसके stick ऊपर the ऊँचाई of the कन्धों or above the क्रॉस बार of a hockey goal.
This can परिणाम in a stoppage of खेल or in a penalty.
in the rules of the नेशनल Hockey लीग, high-sticking is पारिभाषित as a दंड in Rule 60 और as a non-penalty बेईमानी in नियम 80.
A stoppage in play results if a ऊँची स्टिक comes in सम्पर्क with the puck और the team who touched it regains कंट्रोल of the पक.
However, खेल usually continues if a खिलाड़ी touches the पक with a ऊँची स्टिक and the opposing टोली gains control of the पक.
if the पक goes into the opposing net बाद coming into सम्पर्क with a high स्टिक, the लक्ष्य is प्रतिबंधित.
The level at जिससे a स्टिक is माना too ऊँची for a लक्ष्य is the crossbar of the net.
However, if a खिलाड़ी knocks the पक into उसके अपना जाल साथ a high स्टिक, the goal is अनुमत.
a penalty is assessed if a खिलाड़ी हमलों another player with a ऊँची स्टिक.
the खिलाड़ी is दिए a नाबालिग दंड unless his high स्टिक caused an injury, in जिससे मामला the referee has the option to assess a double-minor, major or match penalty.
it is the रेफरी 's discretion which दंड to assess : the नियम काल्स for a दोगुना नाबालिग लिये an आकस्मिक चोट, or a मैच penalty लिये a deliberate attempt to injure ( whether the विपक्ष खिलाड़ी थी दरअसल injured ).
Injury is प्रायः decided by the ऊँची स्टिक causing bleeding, but the उपस्थिति of रक्त does नहीं automatically औसत an extra दंड is awarded.
कुछ referees have been ज्ञात to award an अतिरिक्त दंड बगैर the presence of रक्त if the referee determines that the चोट sustained थी sufficient to warrant a double-minor penalty.
Typical आधुनिक memory कार्ड reader, compatible साथ अनेक आम formats
A मेमोरी card रीडर is a device, typically having a USB interface, लिये accessing the आंकड़ा on a मेमोरी कार्ड ऐसे as a CompactFlash ( cf ), सुरक्षित Digital ( sd ) or multimediacard ( MMC ).
Most कार्ड readers also offer write काबिलियत, और साथ with the कार्ड, this can function as a pen drive.
कुछ मुद्रक and personal कंप्यूटर have a built-in card reader.
a मल्टी card रीडर is प्रयुक्त लिये संचार साथ अधिक than one प्रकार of फ्लैश मेमोरी कार्ड.
Multi कार्ड पाठक do नहीं have built-in memory क्षमता, but are समर्थ to accept अनेक types और शैलियाँ of मेमोरी ताश.
The क्रमांक of संगत memory ताश varies from reader to reader and can शामिल more than 20 different प्रकार.
the क्रमांक of अलग मेमोरी cards कि a मल्टी कार्ड reader can accept is expressed as x-in-1, with x होने a figure of merit indicating the number of memory ताश accepted, ऐसे as 35-in-1.
वहीँ are तीन श्रेणी of कार्ड पाठक sorted by the type और quantity of the कार्ड slots : सिंगल कार्ड रीडर ( e.g. 1x sd-only ), मल्टी card रीडर ( e.g. 9-in-1 ) और श्रेणी कार्ड रीडर ( e.g. 4x SD तभी ).
कुछ kinds of मेमोरी cards with उनके own USB कृत्यों do not need the card reader, such as the बुद्धिमान स्टिक मेमोरी card, जिससे can प्लग सीधे into a usb स्लॉट.

Bullying is हानिकारक to students ' well-being और विकास.
धमकाना is the उपयोग of force or coercion to abuse or intimidate others.
the behavior can be habitual and involve an असंतुलन of सोशल or physical power.
it can शामिल verbal harassment or threat, शारीरिक उत्पीड़न or coercion और may be निर्देशित repeatedly towards particular पीड़ितों, perhaps on grounds of रेस, religion, gender, कामुकता, or ability.
if धमकाना is किया by a group, it is called mobbing.
The शिकार of धमकाना is sometimes referred to as a `` निशाना ''.
धमकाना can be पारिभाषित in अनेक different ways.
The UK फिलहाल has no legal परिभाषा of bullying, जबकि some u.S. states have कानून विरूद्ध it.
Bullying consists of तीन मौलिक प्रकार of abuse – emotional, मौखिक, and physical.
It typically involves हल्का methods of coercion such as intimidation.
धमकाना ranges इससे सरल one-on-one धमकाना to more जटिल धमकाना in जिससे the bully may have एक or more `` lieutenants '' who may seem to be willing to assist the primary बुली in उसके or उसके धमकाना क्रियाएँ.
Bullying in स्कूल और the कार्यस्थल is भी referred to as पीर abuse.
रॉबर्ट W. फुलर रै analyzed bullying in the कॉन्टेक्स्ट of rankism.
A धमकाना culture can develop in कोई context in जिससे human beings interact with प्रत्येक other.
This includes स्कूल, church, family, the workplace, घर, और पड़ोस.

An एम्बर चेतावनी or a चाइल्ड abduction Emergency ( वही कोड : CAE ) is a चाइल्ड abduction चेतावनी system originating in 1996, now employed in 9 देशों.
AMBER is officially a backronym लिये अमेरिका 's Missing : Broadcasting Emergency Response, named लिये एम्बर Hagerman, a 9-year-old abducted और murdered in आर्लिंगटन, Texas in 1996.
Alternate regional चेतावनी names यहूद once used ; in Georgia, `` लेवी 's कॉल '' ( नामित after लेवी frady ) ; in हवाई, `` maile एम्बर Alert '' ( बाद maile गिल्बर्ट ) ; और अरकंसास, `` Morgan उपनाम Amber चेतावनी '' ( in memory of मॉर्गन Chauntel Nick ).
एम्बर Alerts are distributed via वाणिज्यिक radio स्टेशन, Internet रेडियो, उपग्रह रेडियो, टेलीविज़न स्टेशन, और केबल tv by the आपात चेतावनी System and NOAA मौसम Radio ( जहाँ वे हैं termed `` Child abduction Emergency '' or `` Amber Alerts '' ).
The चेतावनियाँ हैं also जारी via e-mail, electronic traffic-condition लक्षण, the LED billboards which are स्तिथ बाहर of नए walgreens स्थितियाँ, along साथ the led/lcd लक्षण of billboard companies such as Clear Channel बाहरी, CBS Outdoor and Lamar, or through wireless device SMS text messages.
एम्बर चेतावनी has also teamed up with Google और फेसबुक to रिले information regarding an AMBER Alert to an कभी growing जनसांख्यिकी.
Those दिलचस्पी in subscribing to प्राप्त AMBER Alerts in their क्षेत्रफल via sms messages can विज़िट बेतार Amber चेतावनियाँ, जिससे are offered by विधि as फ़्री संदेश.
in some states, the प्रदर्शक scrollboards in सामने of lottery terminals are also used.
the decision to declare an एम्बर Alert is made by प्रत्येक police organization ( in अनेक मामले, the state पुलिस or राजमार्ग patrol ) which investigates प्रत्येक of the abductions.
पब्लिक सूचना in an AMBER Alert usually consists of the नाम और description of the abductee, a वर्णन of the suspected abductor, and a description और अनुज्ञा plate क्रमांक of the abductor 's vehicle, if उपलब्धियाँ.

it फ़ॉलो the adventures of zoey Redbird, a sixteen-year-old लड़की जो रै just become a `` fledgling vampyre '' and is जरूरी to attend the हाउस of रात्रि बोर्डिंग school in तुलसा, ओक्लाहोमा.

in यूनानी mythology, the Trojan युद्ध थी waged विरूद्ध the नगर of ट्रॉय by the Achaeans ( यूनानियों ) after Paris of Troy took Helen इससे उसके husband menelaus किंग of स्पार्टा.
The war is एक of the most महत्वपूर्ण events in यूनानी mythology and रै been narrated through अनेक works of यूनानी साहित्य, most notably through होमर 's Iliad and the ओडिसी.
The Iliad relates a भाग of the पिछला साल of the घेरा of ट्रॉय ; the ओडिसी describes Odysseus 's यात्रा home.
Other parts of the युद्ध are contained in a साईकिल of एपिक कविताएं, जिससे have बच through fragments.
Episodes from the युद्ध provided material लिये यूनानी tragedy और अन्य works of यूनानी साहित्य, and लिये रोमन कवियों सहित वर्जिल और Ovid.
The युद्ध originated from a झगड़ा between the देवियाँ Athena, Hera, और aphrodite, after Eris, the goddess of संघर्ष और अनबन, gave उन्हें a golden apple, sometimes known as the ठहराना of Discord, marked `` for the fairest ''.
Zeus sent the देवियाँ to पेरिस, जो judged that aphrodite, as the `` fairest '', चाहिए प्राप्त the ठहराना.
in exchange, Aphrodite बना Helen, the most beautiful of सब women and बीवी of menelaus, fall in love साथ पेरिस, who took उसके to Troy.
agamemnon, king of Mycenae और the bhai of Helen 's husband Menelaus, led an expedition of Achaean सैनिकों to ट्रॉय and besieged the नगर for टेन सालो क्युकी of Paris ' insult.
बाद the मौतों of अनेक heroes, सहित the achaeans Achilles and अजाक्स, and the ट्रोजन्स Hector और पेरिस, the city fell to the ruse of the Trojan Horse.
The Achaeans slaughtered the Trojans ( मगर लिये some of the महिलाओं और children जिसको वे रखा or बेची as स्लेव ) और desecrated the temples, यूँ earning the देवताओं ' प्रकोप.
few of the achaeans returned सकुशल to their घरों and अनेक संस्थापित colonies in दूर shores.
the Romans later traced their उत्पत्ति to aeneas, one of the ट्रोजन्स, who थी कहा to have led the surviving Trojans to modern-day Italy.
the प्राचीन यूनानियों विचार कि the Trojan युद्ध थी a historical event that था लिया प्लेस in the 13th or 12th सदी bc, और believed that ट्रॉय was located in modern-day तुर्कों निकट the Dardanelles.
By आधुनिक टाइम्स, both the war और the नगर यहूद widely believed to be non-historical.
In 1868, however, the जर्मनी पुरातत्ववेत्ताओं heinrich schliemann मिले Frank calvert, जो कायल schliemann कि ट्रॉय थी at Hissarlik and schliemann took over calvert 's excavations on property belonging to Calvert ; this claim is now स्वीकृत by most scholars.
Whether वहीँ is कोई ऐतिहासिक वास्तविकता behind the trojan युद्ध is an open सवाल.
अनेक scholars मानना कि there is a ऐतिहासिक कोर to the टेल, though this may बस औसत कि the homeric stories are a संलयन of विभिन्न किस्से of sieges और expeditions by माइसीनियाई यूनानियों during the कांस्य आयु.
those जो believe that the कहानियां of the trojan War are निकला इससे a specific ऐतिहासिक विरोध प्रायः date it to the 12th or 11th centuries bc, प्रायः preferring the तिथियाँ दिए by इरैटोस्थनिज़, 1194–1184 bc, जिससे roughly corresponds with पुरातत्व प्रमाण of a catastrophic burning of Troy VIIa.
anarchists have employed निश्चित प्रतीकों लिये their कारण, including most prominently the circle-A और the ब्लैक flag, although anarchists have historically largely अस्वीकृत the importance of symbols to political गति.
Since the पुनरुद्धार of anarchism around the प्रारंभ of the 21st-century संयुक्त with the rise of the anti-globalization movement, अराजकतावादी सांस्कृतिक symbols are widely उपस्थित.
The वृहद palatine canal ( or pterygopalatine canal ) is a ड्योढ़ी in the कपाल कि transmits the greater palatine artery, रग, और तंत्रिका between the pterygopalatine fossa and the मौखिक गुहा.
Surface temperature of अंटार्कटिक in शीत and गर्मियाँ from the European Centre for medium-range Weather forecasts
the जलवायु of अंटार्कटिक is the coldest on the whole of धरती.
Antarctica रै the न्यूनतम naturally occurring temperature कभी recorded on the मैदान on Earth : −89.2 °c ( −128.6 °f ) at वोस्तोक स्टेशन.
It is also अत्यधिक शुष्क ( technically a मरुस्थल ), averaging 166 mm ( 6.5 in ) of वर्षण प्रति साल.
भी so, on most parts of the महाद्वीप the हिम rarely melts and is आखिरकार compressed to become the glacial ice that makes up the ice sheet.
मौसम fronts rarely घुस दूर into the महाद्वीप.
सबसे of अंटार्कटिक has an बर्फ कैप जलवायु ( Köppen ef ) with बहुत ठंडा, generally अत्यधिक शुष्क weather throughout the साल और no माह averaging ऊपर 0 °c ( 32 °f ).
