in दण्ड विधि, fraud is जानबूझकर deception made लिये निजी लाभ or to क्षति another individual ; the related adjective is fraudulent, और क्रिया is defraud.
Fraud is a अपराधों और a सिविल law उल्लंघन, though the विशिष्ट criminal law परिभाषा varies by legal क्षेत्राधिकार.
Defrauding लोगों or entities of money or valuables is a आम purpose of धोखाधड़ी.
a hoax also involves deception, but बगैर the intention of लाभ or of damaging or depriving the शिकार.
धोखाधड़ी is a defense in a civil कार्रवाई for उल्लंघन of contract or specific performance of a अनुबंध.
धोखाधड़ी is a आधार लिये equitable क्षेत्राधिकार.
Passover, or pesach ( इससे : in Hebrew, यहूदी ), Tiberian :, Modern यहूदी : /ˈpesaχ/ pesah, Pesakh, Yiddish : Peysekh, paysakh, Paysokh ) is an महत्वपूर्ण Biblically -derived यहूदी festival.
Historically, साथ साथ Shavuot ( `` पेंटेकोस्ट '' ) और sukkot ( `` झोपड़ियों '' ), passover is one of the तीन pilgrimage त्यौहार ( shalosh Regalim ) during जिससे the entire जनसांख्यिकी of the किंगडम of यहूदा made a यात्राएं to the टेम्पल in जेरूसलम.
samaritans स्टिल मेक इस यात्राएं to माउंट gerizim, लकिन तभी मेन participate in पब्लिक इबादत.
passover commences on the 15th of the Hebrew month of Nisan and lasts लिये either सात दिनों ( in इसराईल ) or आठ days ( in the diaspora ).
in judaism, a दिन commences at dusk and lasts जबतक the following dusk, thus the पहला दिन of passover तभी begins बाद संध्या of the 14th of Nisan and ends at संध्या of the 15th day of the month of Nisan.
the rituals unique to the Passover जश्न commence with the Passover Seder जब the 15th of nisan रै begun.
in the Northern गोलार्ध Passover takes प्लेस in spring as the Torah prescribes it : `` in the month of [ the ] वसन्त '' ( בחדש האביב ).
It is एक of the सबसे widely observed यहूदी छुट्टियाँ.
The Jewish लोगों celebrate Passover as a commemoration of उनके liberation over 3,300 सालो पहले by God from गुलामी in प्राचीन मिश्र कि was शासित by the Pharaohs, और their जनम as a स्वदेश अंतर्गत the नेतृत्व of Moses.
it commemorates the स्टोरी of the Exodus as वर्णित in the Hebrew Bible especially in the Book of Exodus, in जिससे the israelites were freed from slavery in मिश्र.
In the कथा of the Exodus, the बाइबल tells कि परमेश्वर helped the Children of Israel एस्केप इससे their slavery in Egypt by inflicting टेन plagues upon the ancient उन्होंने पहले the pharaoh होता रिलीज his israelite स्लेव ; the दसवाँ and worst of the plagues थी the मौत of the मिश्र first-born.
The israelites यहूद instructed to mark the doorposts of उनके घरों साथ the blood of a slaughtered spring मेमने और, upon seeing this, the spirit of the रब knew to pass over the first-born in these homes, hence the name of the holiday.
वहीँ is कुछ बहस over जहाँ the term is दरअसल निकला इससे.
जब the pharaoh freed the israelites, it is said कि वे left in ऐसे a hurry that they could नहीं इंतजार लिये bread dough to rise ( leaven ).
In commemoration, लिये the अवधि of passover no leavened ब्रैड is eaten, लिये जिससे कारण it is called `` the पर्व of the unleavened Bread ''.
यूँ matzo ( चपटा unleavened ब्रैड ) is eaten during passover और it is a प्रतीक of the holiday.
Halley 's धूमकेतु or Comet हैली ( or ), officially designated 1p/halley, is the best-known of the short-period comets और is दृश्य इससे Earth every 75–76 years.
Halley is the तभी short-period धूमकेतु that is clearly visible to the नग्न नजर इससे धरती, और thus the तभी naked-eye comet कि might appear twice in a human आजीवन.
अन्य naked-eye धूमकेतुओं may be उज्जवल और अधिक spectacular, लकिन होगा appear तभी एकबार in हज़ारों of सालो.
Halley 's रिटर्न to the inner सौर प्रणाली have been observed और recorded by खगोलशास्त्रियों चूंकि at least 240 BCE.
साफ रिकॉर्ड of the धूमकेतु 's दिखावे were बना by चाइनीज, babylonian, और मध्यकालीन यूरोपीय chroniclers, लकिन यहूद नहीं पहचाना as reappearances of the वही object at the समय.
The धूमकेतु 's periodicity was first संकल्पित in 1705 by अंग्रेज़ी astronomer edmond Halley, बाद whom it is अभी नामित.
हैली 's धूमकेतु पिछला appeared in the inner सौर प्रणाली in 1986 and will next appear in mid-2061.
During इसके 1986 apparition, हैली became the first comet to be observed in विवरण by spacecraft, providing the पहला observational आंकड़ा on the structure of a comet केंद्रक and the mechanism of कोमा और tail गठन.
ये observations समर्थित a क्रमांक of longstanding hypotheses परिचय धूमकेतु निर्माण, विशेषकर Fred whipple 's `` dirty snowball '' model, जिससे correctly predicted कि Halley होता be रचित of a मिश्रण of volatile ices – ऐसे as जल, carbon डाइऑक्साइड और अमोनिया – and dust.
The missions भी provided data which substantially reformed और reconfigured ये विचार ; लिये instance it is now understood that Halley 's surface is largely composed of dusty, non-volatile सामग्री, and that तभी a small portion of it is icy.
Anti-communism is opposition to communism.
व्यवस्थित anti-communism developed in प्रतिक्रिया to the वृद्धि of साम्यवादी, विशेषकर after the 1917 October क्रान्ति in रूस और reaching वैश्विक dimensions during the ठंडा युद्ध.
Most anti-communists अस्वीकृत the concept of ऐतिहासिक भौतिकवाद, which is a central विचार in मार्क्सवाद.
anti-communists reject the मार्क्सवादी विश्वास कि पूंजीवाद होगा be followed by socialism और communism, बस as सामंतवाद was followed by capitalism.
anti-communists question the validity of the मार्क्सवादी अर्जी कि the socialist राज्य होगा `` wither दूर '' when it becomes unnecessary in a सच्चा कम्युनिस्ट society.
anti-communists argue कि the दमन in the जल्दी सालो of bolshevik नियम, जबकि not as चरम as कि during जोसेफ Stalin 's rule, थी still कठोर by reasonable standards, citing उदाहरण such as फेलिक्स dzerzhinsky 's secret police, which eliminated numerous political प्रतिद्वंद्वियों by extrajudicial executions, and the brutal crushing of the kronstadt विद्रोह और tambov विद्रोह.
Some anti-communists refer to दोनो साम्यवादी और फासीवाद as सर्वसत्तावाद, देखकर similarity between the क्रियाएँ of communist और fascist governments.
Historian रॉबर्ट conquest has argued कि Communism was जिम्मेदार लिये tens of millions of मौतों दौरान the 20th century.
प्रतिद्वंद्वियों argue कि Communist पार्टियों that have आइये to शक्ति have tended to be rigidly असहिष्णु of राजनैतिक opposition.
ये प्रतिद्वंद्वियों claim that सबसे कम्युनिस्ट देशों have shown no लक्षण of advancing इससे मार्क्स 's समाजवादी स्टेज of economy to an ideal communist स्टेज.
बल्कि, कम्युनिस्ट governments have महरूम अभियुक्त of बनाना a new सत्ताधारी क्लास ( a nomenklatura ), साथ शक्तियां and privileges वृहद than those previously enjoyed by the अपर classes in the non- communist regimes.
gil बगुला ( 9 अप्रैल 1922 – 27 नवम्बर 2008 ) थी a Jamaican पेशेवर footballer.
He was the first ब्लैक खिलाड़ी to खेल for Scottish क्लबों सेल्टिक, और थी the पिता of कवि and musician gil Scott-Heron.
He died in डेट्रॉयट of a दिल attack on 27 November 2008.
the सोयाबीन ( us ) or soya bean ( UK ) ( glycine अधिकतम ) is a species of legume native to ईस्ट एशिया, widely grown लिये इसके edible bean जिससे has numerous उपयोग.
The संयंत्र is classed as an oilseed बल्कि than a pulse by the un खाना और agricultural संगठन ( fao ).
Fat-free ( defatted ) soybean भोजन is a significant and cheap सोर्स of प्रोटीन लिये एनिमल फ़ीड्स and many prepackaged meals ; सोया सब्ज़ी oil is another product of processing the सोयाबीन crop.
For उदाहरण, soybean products such as textured सब्ज़ी protein ( tvp ) हैं संघटक in many meat and दुग्ध analogues.
Soybeans उपज significantly अधिक protein प्रति acre than सबसे अन्य uses of land.
परंपरागत nonfermented खाना उपयोग of soybeans शामिल soy milk, और from the latter टोफू और टोफू skin.
fermented भोजन शामिल सोया सॉस, fermented bean paste, natto, और tempeh, among others.
the oil is used in अनेक औद्योगिक अनुप्रयोग.
the प्रमुख निर्माता of सोया are the संयुक्त States ( 35 % ), ब्राज़ील ( 27 % ), अर्जेंटीना ( 19 % ), China ( 6 % ) और इण्डिया ( 4 % ).
The सेम contain significant amounts of phytic acid, alpha-linolenic acid, and isoflavones.

A tube of chapstick
chapstick is a brand नाम लिये लिप बाम manufactured by Pfizer Consumer Healthcare और used in many देशों विश्वव्यापी.
it is intended to help treat and prevent chapped होठ ; hence the name.
Many किस्में भी include सनस्क्रीन in order to prevent sunburn.
due to इसके लोकप्रियता, the term has become a genericized ट्रेडमार्क.
It popularly refers to कोई लिप balm contained in a lipstick-style tube और लागू in the वही manner as lipstick.
however, the term is still a पंजीकृत trademark, साथ rights exclusively स्वामित्व by Pfizer.
In स्वीडन और in the United किंगडम, the उत्पाद 's main प्रतिस्पर्धी is lypsyl, बना by novartis Consumer स्वास्थ्य, जिससे is वितरित in similar पैकेजिंग to chapstick.
जार्ज बर्कली ( ; 12 March 168514 जनवरी 1753 ), also known as बिशप बर्कली ( Bishop of cloyne ), was an Anglo-Irish पारस जिनकी प्राथमिक उपलब्धि थी the advancement of a सिद्धान्त he पुकारा `` immaterialism '' ( later referred to as `` subjective idealism `` by अन्य ).
इस सिद्धान्त झुठलाए the अस्तित्व of सामग्री substance and instead contends that परिचित objects जैसे tables और कुर्सियां are तभी विचार in the minds of perceivers, और as a परिणाम can not मौजूद बगैर होने आभास.
यूँ, as Berkeley famously put it, लिये शारीरिक objects `` esse est percipi '' ( `` to be is to be आभास `` ).
बर्कली is भी ज्ञात for his critique of abstraction, an important आधार in उसके तर्क for immaterialism.
in 1709, बर्कली published उसके first प्रमुख कार्य,, in जिससे he discussed the सीमाएं of human दृष्टि और उन्नत the theory that the proper वस्तुएँ of sight हैं नहीं सामग्री वस्तुएँ, लकिन light और colour.
This foreshadowed his मुख्य philosophical कार्य A treatise concerning the सिद्धान्त of इंसान ज्ञान in 1710 which, बाद its ग़रीब reception, he rewrote in dialogue form and published अंतर्गत the शीर्षक तीन संवाद between hylas and philonous in 1713.
in इस किताब, बर्कली 's दृश्य यहूद represented by Philonous ( Greek : 'प्रेमr of दिमाग ' ), जबकि Hylas ( Greek : 'matter ' ) embodies the आयरिश thinker’s प्रतिद्वंद्वियों, in particular John locke.
Berkeley argued against सर इसहाक़ Newton 's doctrine of absolute space, time और गति in De Motu ( on Motion ), published 1721.
His arguments were a precursor to the views of Mach और Einstein.
in 1732, he प्रकाशित Alciphron, a ईसाई क्षमाप्रार्थी against the free-thinkers, और in 1734, he प्रकाशित the Analyst, an empiricist critique of the foundations of infinitesimal कलन, which was influential in the विकास of गणित.
उसके पिछला प्रमुख philosophical कार्य, siris ( 1744 ), begins by वकालत the औषधीय उपयोग of तारकोल water, and तब continues to discuss a wide range of विषय including science, दर्शनशास्त्र, और theology.
ब्याज in Berkeley 's कार्य increased बाद संसार युद्ध II, because he tackled many of the मुद्दे of paramount ब्याज to दर्शनशास्त्र in the 20th century ऐसे as the समस्याएं of perception, the अंतर between प्राथमिक and secondary qualities, और the महत्व of भाषा.
चिंगदाओ ( ), historically known as Tsingtao, is a प्रमुख city in पूर्वी शानदोंग प्रांत, पूर्वी China, with a जनसांख्यिकी of over 8.715 लाख ( 2010 census ).
Its निर्मित up area, made of 6 urban जिले and 4 county-level cities, is home to परिचय 4,896,000 निवासियों in 2010.
It borders yantai to the पूर्वोत्तर, Weifang to the वेस्ट और Rizhao to the southwest.
qīng ( ) in चाइनीज अर्थात् `` ग्रीन '' or `` lush '', while dǎo ( ) अर्थात् `` द्वीप ''.
Qingdao is administered at the sub-provincial level.
Lying आरपार the शानदोंग प्रायद्वीप जबकि looking आउट to the पीला समुद्र, चिंगदाओ is a प्रमुख seaport, naval base, and औद्योगिक केन्द्र.
it is also the साईट of the tsingtao ब्रेवरी.
The संसार 's longest समुद्र सेतु, the चिंगदाओ Haiwan सेतु, कड़ी the main शहरी area of चिंगदाओ with huangdao district, straddling the jiaozhou खाड़ी sea areas.
Qingdao is नामित China 's सबसे livable नगर.
Mimivirus is a viral genus containing a single पहचाना species named acanthamoeba polyphaga mimivirus ( APMV ), or is a group of phylogenetically related large viruses ( designated प्रायः mimin ).
in colloquial speech, apmv is more commonly referred to as बस `` mimivirus ''.
जबतक अक्तूबर 2011, जब a larger virus megavirus chilensis was वर्णित, it had the largest capsid diameter of all ज्ञात viruses.
Mimivirus रै a large and जटिल genome compared with सबसे अन्य वाइरस.
mimivirus, short for `` mimicking microbe '', is so called to प्रतिबिंबित इसके विशाल आकार और apparent Gram-staining गुण.
The मैक्सिकन युद्ध of Independence ( 1810–1821 ) थी an armed conflict between the लोगों of मैक्सिको और the Spanish औपनिवेशिक अधिकारियों जिससे प्रारंभ on सितंबर 16, 1810.
the movement, which became ज्ञात as the मैक्सिकन War of स्वतंत्रता, was led by mexican-born spaniards, Mestizos और amerindians जो sought independence इससे स्पेन.
it started as an idealistic peasants ' rebellion against उनके colonial मास्टर्स, लकिन ended as an असंभावित गठबंधन between Mexican ex-royalists and Mexican छापामार insurgents.
crohn 's बीमारी, भी ज्ञात as crohn syndrome and क्षेत्रीय enteritis, is a प्रकार of inflammatory bowel disease कि may affect कोई भाग of the जठरांत्र tract इससे मुँह to गुदा, causing a wide variety of लक्षण.
it primarily कल्याणकारी abdominal pain, diarrhea ( जिससे may be bloody if inflammation is at इसके worst ), उल्टी ( can be निरन्तर ), or weight घाटा, लकिन may also cause complications बाहर the gastrointestinal ट्रैक्ट such as skin rashes, गठिया, inflammation of the नजर, थकान, और कमी of concentration.

This परिणाम in a chronic inflammatory disorder, in जिससे the body 's प्रतिरक्षा प्रणाली attacks the जठरांत्र ट्रैक्ट possibly directed at सूक्ष्मजैविक antigens.
Crohn 's disease रै wrongly महरूम described as an असंक्राम्य disease in the पास्ट ; हाल investigators have वर्णित it as an immune कमियां राज्य.

Siblings of प्रभावित individuals are at उच्चतर risk.
Males and females हैं बराबर प्रभावित.

Crohn 's disease affects between 400,000 और 600,000 लोगों in North अमेरिका.

Microsoft डाइरेक्टएक्स is a संग्रहण of अनुप्रयोग प्रोग्रामिंग interfaces ( APIs ) लिये हैंडलिंग tasks सम्बन्धित to multimedia, विशेषकर game प्रोग्रामिंग और वीडियो, on Microsoft platforms.
originally, the names of ये api सब began with सीधा, such as direct3d, DirectDraw, directmusic, DirectPlay, directsound, और so forth.
the name डाइरेक्टएक्स was coined as आशुलिपि पद लिये सब of these APIs ( the x standing in लिये the particular api names ) और जल्द became the name of the संग्रहण.
जब microsoft बाद नियत आउट to develop a गेमिंग कंसोल, the X थी प्रयुक्त as the basis of the name एक्सबॉक्स to indicate कि the console थी based on DirectX प्रौद्योगिकी.
The x आरंभिक has महरूम carried आगे in the नामकरण of api designed for the एक्सबॉक्स such as xinput और the Cross-platform Audio सृष्टि औजार ( XACT ), जबकि the डाइरेक्टएक्स pattern has महरूम जारी लिये खिड़कियाँ api ऐसे as Direct2D और DirectWrite.
Direct3D ( the 3d ग्राफिक्स api within DirectX ) is widely used in the development of वीडियो games for microsoft खिड़कियाँ, Microsoft एक्सबॉक्स, Microsoft Xbox 360 और some sega Dreamcast खेल.
direct3d is भी प्रयुक्त by अन्य तन्त्र applications लिये visualization और ग्राफिक्स tasks such as cad/cam engineering.
as direct3d is the सबसे widely publicized घटक of डाइरेक्टएक्स, it is आम to see the names `` डाइरेक्टएक्स '' and `` direct3d '' प्रयुक्त interchangeably.
the डाइरेक्टएक्स तन्त्र development kit ( SDK ) consists of runtime libraries in redistributable शब्दकोष रूप, साथ साथ accompanying दस्तावेज़ीकरण और headers लिये use in कोडिंग.
originally, the runtimes यहूद only संस्थापित by games or explicitly by the उपयोक्ता.
Windows 95 किया नहीं launch with DirectX, लकिन डाइरेक्टएक्स was शामिल साथ खिड़कियाँ 95 oem सेवा रिलीज 2.
Windows 98 and Windows NT 4.0 दोनो shipped साथ डाइरेक्टएक्स, as रै प्रत्येक संस्करण of खिड़कियाँ released चूंकि.
the SDK is उपलब्धियाँ as a फ़्री download.
While the runtimes हैं proprietary, closed-source तन्त्र, source code is provided लिये सबसे of the sdk samples.
Starting साथ the release of खिड़कियाँ 8 डेवलपर पूर्वावलोकन, डाइरेक्टएक्स SDK रै been integrated into Windows SDK.
direct3d 9Ex, Direct3D 10, और direct3d 11 are तभी available for खिड़कियाँ विस्टा and newer क्युकी each of ये new versions थी निर्मित to निर्भर upon the new खिड़कियाँ Display ड्राइवर Model that थी introduced for Windows विस्टा.
The नई vista/wddm ग्राफिक्स architecture शामिल a नई video मेमोरी मैनेजर supporting आभासीकरण of ग्राफिक्स hardware लिये various applications and सेवाएं like the Desktop खिड़की मैनेजर.

the एपिक of gilgamesh, an epic कविता इससे Mesopotamia, is amongst the earliest surviving works of literature.
the literary इतिहास of gilgamesh begins साथ पाँच स्वतंत्र Sumerian कविताएं about 'bilgamesh ' ( Sumerian for Gilgamesh ), king of Uruk.
चार of ये were प्रयुक्त as सोर्स सामग्री for a combined एपिक in अक्कादी.
इस पहला संयुक्त epic, ज्ञात as the `` Old babylonian '' version, तिथियाँ to the 18th सदी bc और is titled after इसके incipit, shūtur eli sharrī ( `` Surpassing All Other Kings '' ).
Only a few fragments of it have बच.
the later `` Standard Babylonian '' संस्करण तिथियाँ इससे the 13th to the 10th सदियां bc और bears the incipit शा naqba īmuru ( `` he जो देखी the गहन '' ).
fragments of लगभग two तिहाई of this longer, twelve-tablet संस्करण have been बरामद.
कुछ of the बेहतरीन नक़ल यहूद discovered in the पुस्तकालयों ruins of the 7th-century bc assyrian किंग ashurbanipal.
the स्टोरी centers on a friendship between gilgamesh और enkidu.
Enkidu is a wild man निर्मित by the देवताओं as gilgamesh 's equal to distract उसे इससे oppressing the people of uruk.
Together, वे यात्रा to the Cedar पहाड़ to शिकस्त humbaba, इसके monstrous संरक्षक.
बाद वे kill the सांड of Heaven, जिससे the देवी इश्तार sends to सजा gilgamesh for spurning उसके अग्रिम.
as a punishment लिये these क्रियाएँ, the देवताओं वाक्य enkidu to मौत.
the second हाफ of the एपिक focuses on gilgamesh 's distress at enkidu 's मौत, and his quest for अमरत्व.
in अनुक्रम to learn the secret of अनन्त जीवन, gilgamesh undertakes a long और perilous यात्रा.
he learns that `` the जीवन कि तुम हैं seeking you will never find.
जब the देवताओं निर्मित man वे allotted to him death, लकिन जीवन वे retained in उनके अपना keeping. ''
इस quote was originally attributed to siduri in the बूढ़ा Babylonian version of the एपिक, and तब attributed to the अमर बाढ़ hero Utnapishtim in the अक्कादी संस्करण of the एपिक.
nevertheless, gilgamesh 's fame lived on after his मौत, because of his ग्रेट building प्रोजेक्ट, और उसके खाता of कया utnapishtim बताई उसे happened during the बाढ़.
the स्टोरी रै been अनूदित into many different भाषाएं, और gilgamesh रै since become adapted in works of popular fiction.
वहीँ हैं numerous debates over who निर्मित the पहला video खेल, with the जवाब depending largely on कैसा video games are पारिभाषित.

आंकड़ा निष्पादन रोकथाम ( dep ) is a security विशेषता शामिल in modern operating प्रणालियों.
It is known to be उपलब्धियाँ in लिनक्स, Mac os x, आईओएस, microsoft खिड़कियाँ और Android ऑपरेटिंग प्रणालियों और is intended to prevent an application or service इससे निष्पादित कोड from a non-executable मेमोरी प्रदेश.
इस helps prevent निश्चित कारनामे कि स्टोर कोड via a buffer अतिप्रवाह, लिये उदाहरण.
dep रनों in दो modes : hardware-enforced dep for CPUs that can mark मेमोरी पृष्ठों as nonexecutable, and software-enforced dep साथ limited protection for cpu कि do not have hardware support.
software-enforced DEP does नहीं protect विरूद्ध निष्पादन of कोड in आंकड़ा पृष्ठों, but instead counters SEH मिटाकर, another प्रकार of आक्रमण.
dep थी introduced on Linux in 2004 ( कर्नेल 2.6.8 ), on खिड़कियाँ in 2004 साथ खिड़कियाँ xp सेवा पैक 2, जबकि ठहराना introduced dep जब वे moved to x86 in 2006.

But in आज 's language it refers almost exclusively for वर्ण who have an overall feminine appearance.
in कि case the पद is भी प्रायः abbreviated as futa ( s ), जिससे is occasionally भी used as पद लिये the works itself.
जल्दी captchas ऐसे as ये, generated by the EZ-Gimpy कार्यक्रम, यहूद प्रयुक्त on याहू !
a आधुनिक CAPTCHA, rather than attempting to बनाएँ a distorted background and high levels of warping on the text, might फ़ोकस on making segmentation मुश्किल by adding an angled line.
another रास्ता to make segmentation difficult is to भीड symbols साथ, as in याहू ! 's current CAPTCHA format.
कुछ CAPTCHAs try to utilize the ability of people to देखिए three-dimensional objects.
On this चित्र, symbols are drawn with लाइनों of different मोटाई to make an प्रभाव of extrusion.
a captcha ( ) is a प्रकार of challenge-response test used in computing as an attempt to ensure कि the जवाब is generated by a इंसान being.
the process usually involves a computer asking a उपयोक्ता to पूरा a simple परीक्षण which the कंप्यूटर is समर्थ to grade.
ये tests हैं designed to be आसान लिये a कंप्यूटर to generate लकिन मुश्किल लिये a कंप्यूटर to solve, लकिन again आसान लिये a human.
If a सही समाधान is received, it can be presumed to have been डाला by a इंसान.
a आम type of captcha requires the उपयोक्ता to प्रकार अक्षर and/or अंक from a distorted image that appears on the screen.
ऐसे परीक्षण are commonly used to prevent अनावश्यक internet बॉट from accessing वेबसाइटों, since a सामान्य human can easily पढ़ा a CAPTCHA, while the bot can not प्रक्रम the चित्र letters and therefore, can नहीं जवाब properly, or at सब.
Although सबसे CAPTCHAs हैं अक्षर तस्वीरें randomly generated, अनेक of them have become मुश्किल भी for a इंसान to पढ़ा, so picture CAPTCHAs यहूद created in जिससे a इंसान is shown a सरल test to दिखाएँ a picture of a निश्चित animal ( दिए few एनिमल pictures ), जिससे is simple for a human होने to process, और therefore easy to चुनें, जबकि a bot can not process और solve the सवाल क्युकी हालांकि it can analyze the चित्र, it can नहीं easily guess the एनिमल.
The पद `` CAPTCHA '' was coined in 2000 by लुइस von ahn, मैनुएल ब्लम, निकोलस J. हॉपर, and जॉन Langford ( all of Carnegie Mellon विश्वविद्यालयों ).
it is an एक्रोनिम आधारित on the शब्द `` capture '' and standing लिये `` completely स्वचालित Public turing परीक्षण to बताना कंप्यूटर and Humans Apart ''.
Carnegie Mellon विश्वविद्यालयों attempted to ट्रेडमार्क the term on 15 अक्तूबर 2004, but the ट्रेडमार्क अनुप्रयोग was abandoned on 21 April 2008.
A captcha is sometimes described as a रिवर्स turing test, क्युकी it is administered by a यंत्र and targeted at a human, in contrast to the standard Turing परीक्षण कि is typically administered by a इंसान और targeted at a यंत्र.

he co-developed the Aqua-Lung, pioneered समुद्री conservation और थी a member of the Académie française.
केएफसी ( केंटकी Fried मुर्गा ) is a fast food रेस्तरां chain headquartered in louisville, केंटकी, संयुक्त राज्य, जिससे specializes in fried मुर्गा.
an `` अमरीकी icon '', it is the संसार 's दूसरी largest restaurant कड़ी overall ( as measured by बिक्री ) बाद McDonald 's, with over 18,000 outlets in 120 देशों और territories.
the company is a subsidiary of यम !
Brands, a रेस्तरां company which भी owns Pizza Hut और टैको घंटी.
KFC थी संस्थापित by Harland सैंडर्स, who began selling fried मुर्गा इससे उसके roadside restaurant in कोर्बिन, केंटकी during the ग्रेट अवसाद.
Sanders थी एक of the पहला people to see the potential of the restaurant फ़्रेंचाइज़िंग concept, साथ the पहला `` केंटकी fried मुर्गा '' मताधिकार opening in यूटा in 1952.
The franchise popularized chicken in the तेज़ खाना उद्योग, thereby diversifying the market and चुनौतीपूर्ण the दबदबा of the hamburger.
विपणन खुद as `` कर्नल Sanders '', he became a legendary फिगर of American cultural इतिहास, और his चित्र is still prominently प्रयुक्त in KFC branding.
the company 's रैपिड विस्तार देखी it grow too large लिये सैंडर्स to manage, and in 1964 he बेची the कम्पनी to a group of investors led by John y. भूरा, Jr. और Jack Massey.
केएफसी थी one of the first fast food जंजीरों to expand internationally, खोलने outlets in इंग्लैण्ड, मैक्सिको and प्यूर्टो Rico by the mid-1960s.
throughout the 1970s और 1980s, KFC experienced mixed fortunes domestically, as it went through a series of corporate owners who had छोटी or no अनुभव in the रेस्तरां business.
in the early 1970s, KFC थी sold to the आत्माओं कड़ Heublein, जो were लिया over by the R.J. Reynolds खाना और tobacco संगुटिका, जो बेची the कड़ी to पेप्सिको.
the chain जारी to expand विदेशी however, and in 1987 केएफसी became the पहला पश्चिमी रेस्तरां कड़ी to खोलें in चीन.
The chain रै since विस्तारित rapidly in चीन, और the country is now the कम्पनी 's सबसे profitable मार्केट.
PepsiCo spun बंद इसके restaurants division as tricon वैश्विक रेस्तरां, which बाद बदला इसके नाम to यम !
Brands.
केएफसी primarily बिकता fried मुर्गा टुकड़े और विसंगतियाँ ऐसे as chicken sandwiches और wraps, सलाद और पक्ष dishes such as फ्रेंच फ्राइज़ and coleslaw, desserts and soft drinks, प्रायः supplied by पेप्सिको.
इसके most famous उत्पाद is दबाव fried मुर्गा टुकड़े, seasoned with Sanders ' `` Original रेसिपी '' of 11 herbs और spices.
The सटीक nature of ये ingredients is अनजान, and represents a notable व्यापार secret.

KFC is प्रसिद्ध लिये the slogan `` finger lickin ' good '', which रै since महरूम replaced by `` Nobody does मुर्गा जैसे KFC '' and `` so good ''.
Cnidaria ( साथ a मूक c ) or coelenterata is a phylum containing over 10,000 प्रजाति of पशु मिला exclusively in जलीय and mostly समुद्री environments.
उनके distinguishing feature is cnidocytes, specialized cells that वे उपयोग मुख्यतः लिये capturing शिकार.
Their bodies consist of mesoglea, a non-living jelly-like पदार्थ, sandwiched between दो layers of epithelium कि are ज़्यादातर one cell मोटा.
They have दो मौलिक देह फ़ॉर्म : swimming medusae and स्थानबद्ध polyps, दोनो of जिससे हैं radially सममित साथ mouths surrounded by tentacles that भालू cnidocytes.
Both फ़ॉर्म have a सिंगल orifice और body गुहा कि हैं प्रयुक्त लिये पाचन और श्वसन.
Many cnidarian प्रजाति produce colonies कि हैं सिंगल जीवों composed of medusa-like or polyp-like zooids, or दोनो.
Cnidarians ' क्रियाएँ हैं समन्वित by a decentralized nerve जाल और सरल receptors.
अनेक free-swimming Cubozoa और Scyphozoa possess balance-sensing statocysts, और some have सरल आँखें.
Not सब cnidarians reproduce sexually.
Many have जटिल lifecycles साथ अलैंगिक polyp चरण and यौन medusae, but कुछ omit either the polyp or the medusa stage.
cnidarians यहूद for a long time grouped साथ ctenophores in the phylum coelenterata, लकिन increasing जागरूकता of उनके मतभेद caused उन्हें to be लगाई in separate phyla.
cnidarians हैं वर्गीकृत into चार प्रमुख groups : the almost wholly स्थानबद्ध Anthozoa ( समुद्र anemones, corals, sea पेन ) ; swimming scyphozoa ( जेलीफ़िश ) ; cubozoa ( बक्सा jellies ) ; और Hydrozoa, a diverse समूह कि शामिल all the freshwater cnidarians as well as many marine forms, और रै दोनो sessile सदस्यों such as Hydra और औपनिवेशिक swimmers such as the Portuguese Man o ' युद्ध.
Staurozoa have recently महरूम recognised as a क्लास in उनके अपना सही बल्कि than a sub-group of scyphozoa, and there is debate परिचय whether myxozoa और polypodiozoa हैं cnidarians or closer to bilaterians ( more जटिल पशु ).
सबसे cnidarians शिकार on जीवों ranging in size इससे प्लवक to पशु several times larger than themselves, लकिन अनेक obtain much of उनके पोषण इससे endosymbiotic algae, और a few are परजीवी.
Many are preyed upon by अन्य animals सहित starfish, sea slugs, मछली and turtles.
मूँगा reefs, whose polyps हैं समृद्ध in endosymbiotic शैवाल, support कुछ of the world 's सबसे productive ecosystems, and protect vegetation in tidal zones और on shorelines इससे दमदार currents और tides.
While corals हैं लगभग entirely प्रतिबंधित to warm, उथले समुद्री waters, अन्य cnidarians सजीव in the गहराइयों, in polar समंदर and in freshwater.
चट्टान cnidarians have been मिला in रॉक्स formed परिचय, और other जीवाश्मों दिखाएँ कि corals may have महरूम उपस्थित shortly before और diversified a few million years later.
Fossils of cnidarians that do not निर्माण mineralized structures are बहुत विरल.
वैज्ञानिकों currently सोचो कि cnidarians, ctenophores and bilaterians हैं अधिक closely सम्बन्धित to calcareous sponges than these हैं to other sponges, और कि anthozoans are the evolutionary `` aunts '' or `` बहनों '' of अन्य cnidarians, और the most closely सम्बन्धित to bilaterians.
हाल analyses have concluded कि cnidarians, although considered अधिक `` primitive '' than bilaterians, have a wider range of जीनों.

the एज़टेक लोगों were निश्चित ethnic समूह of central Mexico, विशेषकर those groups जो spoke the नावातल language और जो वर्चस्व विशाल भाग of मेसोअमेरिका इससे the 14th to 16th सदियां.
the Nahuatl शब्द aztecatl ( एकवचन ) and aztecah ( बहुवचन ) औसत `` people इससे aztlan ``, a पौराणिक प्लेस लिये the Nahuatl-speaking संस्कृति of the time, and later adopted as the शब्द to define the Mexica लोगों.
प्रायः the पद `` एज़टेक '' refers exclusively to the mexica लोगों of Tenochtitlan ( now the स्थान of मैक्सिको City ), situated on an द्वीप in झील Texcoco, जो referred to themselves as mexica tenochca or Cōlhuah Mexica.
sometimes the term भी शामिल the inhabitants of Tenochtitlan 's two principal अलाइड city-states, the acolhuas of texcoco और the Tepanecs of tlacopan, जो together with the mexica formed the Aztec ट्रिपल Alliance जिससे controlled कया is प्रायः ज्ञात as `` the एज़टेक साम्राज्य ''.
in अन्य contexts, Aztec may refer to all the various नगर states और उनके peoples, जो shared विशाल भाग of उनके ethnic इतिहास और सांस्कृतिक traits with the mexica, Acolhua और tepanecs, और जो प्रायः भी used the नावातल भाषा as a lingua फ़्रांका.
in इस अर्थ it is संभावित to बात about an एज़टेक सभ्यता सहित सब the particular सांस्कृतिक patterns आम लिये सबसे of the peoples inhabiting सेंट्रल Mexico in the late postclassic period.
इससे the 13th सदी, the Valley of मैक्सिको थी the दिल of एज़टेक civilization : यहाँ the पूंजी of the Aztec Triple गठबंधन, the नगर of Tenochtitlan, was built upon उठाया आइलेट in झील texcoco.
the ट्रिपल गठबंधन formed a उपनदी साम्राज्य expanding its राजनैतिक आधिपत्य दूर परे the घाटी of मैक्सिको, conquering अन्य नगर states throughout मेसोअमेरिका.
at its शिखर, Aztec culture had समृद्ध और complex पौराणिक और धार्मिक traditions, as खूब as reaching उल्लेखनीय architectural and artistic accomplishments.
in 1521 hernán Cortés, साथ साथ a विशाल क्रमांक of नावातल speaking indigenous allies, conquered tenochtitlan और पराजित the एज़टेक Triple गठबंधन under the leadership of hueyi Tlatoani Moctezuma II.
subsequently the स्पेनी संस्थापित the new settlement of Mexico नगर on the site of the ruined एज़टेक पूंजी, इससे where वे proceeded साथ the प्रक्रम of colonizing सेंट्रल America.
Aztec संस्कृति and इतिहास is primarily ज्ञात through archaeological प्रमाण found in excavations ऐसे as कि of the renowned Templo Mayor in मैक्सिको City ; इससे स्वदेशी छाल पेपर codices ; from eyewitness accounts by Spanish conquistadors such as hernán cortés and Bernal Díaz डेल कैस्टिलो ; और विशेषकर इससे 16th और 17th सदी descriptions of Aztec culture और इतिहास written by Spanish clergymen and साक्षर aztecs in the Spanish or नावातल language, ऐसे as the प्रसिद्ध Florentine codex compiled by the franciscan भिक्षु bernardino de sahagún with the सहायता of स्वदेशी Aztec informants.

a प्लाट of a normal वितरण ( or bell-shaped curve ) where each band रै a width of 1 मानक विचलन – देखिए also : 68-95-99.7 नियम
Cumulative probability of a सामान्य वितरण with अपेक्षित value 0 and standard deviation 1.
in आंकडे and संभाव्यता सिद्धान्त, मानक विचलन ( represented by the प्रतीक सिग्मा, σ ) shows how much विभिन्नता or dispersion exists इससे the औसत ( mean ), or अपेक्षित मान.
A low standard विचलन indicates कि the आंकड़ा अंक tend to be very बंद to the mean ; high standard deviation indicates कि the आंकड़ा अंक are स्प्रेड out over a विशाल दायरा of values.
the मानक विचलन of a यादृच्छिक परिवर्तनीय, सांख्यिकीय जनसांख्यिकी, आंकड़ा set, or probability distribution is the वर्गाकार root of इसके variance.
it is algebraically simpler though practically कम robust than the औसत absolute deviation.
a useful प्रॉपर्टी of मानक deviation is कि, unlike variance, it is expressed in the वही इकाई as the data.
नोट, however, that लिये माप with percentage as ईकाई, the मानक विचलन होगा have percentage अंक as ईकाई.
In जोड to expressing the variability of a जनसांख्यिकी, standard विचलन is commonly प्रयुक्त to measure विश्वास in सांख्यिकीय conclusions.
For example, the margin of गलती in polling data is determined by calculating the अपेक्षित मानक विचलन in the परिणाम if the same poll यहूद to be conducted अनेक टाइम्स.
the reported हाशिया of गलती is typically परिचय twice the standard deviation ­– the radius of a 95 percent विश्वास अंतराल.
In science, researchers commonly रपट the standard deviation of experimental data, और तभी प्रभाव that fall दूर outside the range of standard deviation हैं considered statistically significant – normal यादृच्छिक गलती or विभिन्नता in the माप is in इस रास्ता distinguished इससे causal विभिन्नता.
मानक deviation is भी important in finance, where the standard deviation on the rate of return on an investment is a माप of the volatility of the निवेश.
When तभी a sample of आंकड़ा इससे a जनसांख्यिकी is available, the मानक deviation of the population can be estimated by a परिवर्धित quantity called the `` नमूना standard विचलन ''.
जब the नमूना is the entire population, इसके unmodified मानक विचलन is पुकारा the `` जनसांख्यिकी मानक विचलन ''.
ulluco ( u : ju : kɔ : ) ( Ullucus tuberosus ) is a संयंत्र grown primarily as a root सब्ज़ी, secondarily as a पत्ता सब्ज़ी.
the ulluco is एक of the most widely grown और economically important रूट फसलों in the Andean प्रदेश of South अमेरिका, दूसरी only to the आलू.
it is known there साथ the common नाम of papa lisa, लकिन also by the क्षेत्रीय names melloco ( इक्वाडोर ), olluco ( Peru ), chugua ( Colombia ) or ruba ( Venezuela ), among others.
the पत्ता और the tuber हैं खाद्य, समान to spinach और the potato, क्रमशः.
वे हैं ज्ञात to contain ऊँची levels of प्रोटीन, कैल्सियम, and carotene.
papalisa यहूद used by the Incas prior to arrival of europeans in दक्षिण America.

The भगोड़े Slave विधि or भगोड़े स्लेव Act was passed by the United राज्य कॉंग्रेस on September 18, 1850, as part of the सुलह of 1850 between Southern slave-holding रूचि and Northern Free-Soilers.
This was एक of the most controversial acts of the 1850 सुलह और heightened Northern fears of a `` slave शक्ति षड्यंत्र ''.
it declared कि सब runaway slaves यहूद, upon capture, to be returned to उनके मास्टर्स.
abolitionists nicknamed it the `` Bloodhound विधि '' लिये the dogs that यहूद used to track bas runaway स्लेव.

the United States federal अर्जित income कर क्रेडिट or अर्जित आय credit ( EITC or eic ) is a refundable कर credit लिये low- और medium-income individuals and couples, primarily लिये those जो have qualifying children.
जब the क्रेडिट exceeds the राशि of कर owed, it results in a कर refund to those जो अर्जी the क्रेडिट.
इस क्रेडिट is provided to offset the बोझ of social सुरक्षा कर और also to प्रचार an प्रोत्साहन to कार्य.
In अनुक्रम लिये a व्यक्ति or युगल to अर्जी one or अधिक व्यक्तियों as उनके qualifying चाइल्ड ( ren ), the आयु, संबंध, and साझा residency आवश्यकताएँ जरूर be मिले, as खूब as some other requirements.
U.S. कर फ़ॉर्म 1040ez, 1040A, or 1040 can be प्रयुक्त to claim eic without qualifying children.
to claim the क्रेडिट साथ qualifying children, 1040A or 1040 जरूर be प्रयुक्त, as खूब as attaching Schedule eic.
eic phases in slowly, रै a medium-length plateau, and तब phases out अधिक slowly than it phased in.
चूंकि the क्रेडिट phases आउट at 21 % ( for two children and लिये तीन or अधिक qualilfying children ) or 16 % ( लिये one qualifying चाइल्ड ), it is सदा preferable to have एक अधिक डालर of actual सैलरी or मजदूरी ( हालांकि technically, चूंकि the EIC तालिका चालें by fifty dollar increments, it 's सदा अस्तबलों to have an extra fifty-dollar वृद्धि of सैलरी or मजदूरी ).
लिये tax साल 2011, the maximum EIC for a सिंगल व्यक्ति or युगल दाखिल without qualifying children was $ 464.
the अधिकतम eic साथ one qualifying चाइल्ड थी $ 3,094, साथ दो children was $ 5,112, और साथ तीन or अधिक qualifying children थी $ 5,751.
ये amounts हैं indexed annually लिये महंगाई.
the अर्जित income कर क्रेडिट रै been भाग of राजनैतिक debates in the संयुक्त राज्य regarding whether raising the न्यूनतम मजदूरी or increasing eic will बेहतर पता a seeming shortage of good-paying jobs.

developmental मनोविज्ञान is the scientific पढ़ाई of परिवर्तन कि occur in इंसान beings over the course of उनके जीवन स्पैन.
Originally concerned with infants और children, the फ़ील्ड रै विस्तारित to शामिल adolescence, वयस्क development, aging, और the entire life स्पैन.
इस field examines बदलें आरपार a व्यापक दायरा of विषय सहित मोटर कौशल और अन्य psycho-physiological प्रक्रियाओं ; संज्ञानात्मक development involving क्षेत्रों ऐसे as प्रॉब्लम solving, moral समझना, और conceptual understanding ; language अधिग्रहण ; सोशल, व्यक्तित्व, और emotional development ; and self-concept और पहचान गठन.
Developmental psychology शामिल issues ऐसे as the extent to which विकास occurs through the gradual accumulation of knowledge versus stage-like विकास, or the extent to which children are born with स्वाभाविक mental structures versus सीखना through अनुभव.
Many researchers हैं interested in the interaction between निजी characteristics, the व्यक्तिगत 's behavior, और पर्यावरणीय कारकों सहित सोशल कॉन्टेक्स्ट, और their प्रभाव on विकास ; others लो a more narrowly-focused दृष्टिकोण.
developmental मनोविज्ञान informs अनेक applied fields, including : educational मनोविज्ञान, child psychopathology, and forensic developmental psychology.
developmental psychology complements अनेक अन्य मौलिक research fields in psychology सहित सोशल psychology, संज्ञानात्मक मनोविज्ञान, ecological मनोविज्ञान, और तुलनात्मक मनोविज्ञान.

The Declaration of Independence is a statement adopted by the महाद्वीपीय कॉंग्रेस on जुलाई 4, 1776, जिससे announced कि the तेरह अमरीकी colonies, then at युद्ध साथ ग्रेट Britain, regarded themselves as स्वतंत्र states, और no longer a part of the British साम्राज्य.
बजाय वे now formed a new nation—the संयुक्त States of अमेरिका.
जॉन Adams was a नेता in pushing for स्वतंत्रता, which was unanimously स्वीकृत on जुलाई 2.
a कमेटी था already drafted the formal घोषणा, to be तैयार जब कॉंग्रेस voted on स्वतंत्रता.
एडम्स persuaded the committee to select थामस जेफरसन to लिखें the असली ड्राफ्ट of the दस्तावेज़, जिससे congress होता संपादन to उपज the फाइनल संस्करण.
the Declaration थी ultimately a औपचारिक explanation of क्यों कॉंग्रेस था voted on जुलाई 2 to declare independence from ग्रेट Britain, अधिक than a year बाद the outbreak of the American क्रांतिकारी War.
The national birthday, the स्वतंत्रता दिन is मनाये on जुलाई 4, हालांकि एडम्स wanted जुलाई 2.
After ratifying the टेक्स्ट on जुलाई 4, कॉंग्रेस जारी the घोषणा of स्वतंत्रता in अनेक forms.
it थी initially published as the printed डनलप broadside कि थी widely वितरित और पढ़ा to the पब्लिक.
The सबसे famous संस्करण of the घोषणा, a signed नक़ल that is popularly regarded as the Declaration of स्वतंत्रता, is displayed at the नेशनल Archives in Washington, D.C.
हालांकि the wording of the घोषणा थी approved on जुलाई 4, the date of इसके signing was August 2.
the original July 4 United राज्य Declaration of Independence पाण्डुलिपि थी lost while सब अन्य copies have been derived इससे this original दस्तावेज़.
the स्त्रोत and interpretation of the घोषणा have been the subject of much scholarly inquiry.
The घोषणा जायज the independence of the United राज्य by listing colonial grievances विरूद्ध King George iii, and by asserting निश्चित प्राकृतिक और विधिक अधिकारों, सहित a सही of revolution.
having परोसा its असली purpose in announcing स्वतंत्रता, the टेक्स्ट of the घोषणा थी initially ignored बाद the अमरीकी क्रान्ति.
Since तब, it रै आइये to be माना a प्रमुख बयान on इंसान rights, particularly इसके second sentence:
We थाम ये truths to be self-evident, कि सब मेन हैं निर्मित equal, कि they हैं endowed by their Creator with निश्चित unalienable Rights, कि among ये are जीवन, स्वतंत्रता and the pursuit of Happiness.
इस has महरूम called `` एक of the best-known वाक्य in the English भाषा '', containing `` the सबसे potent और consequential शब्द in American history. ''
the ड्योढ़ी came to represent a moral मानक to which the United राज्य should strive.
इस view was notably प्रचारित by अब्राहम Lincoln, जो माना the Declaration to be the foundation of उसके राजनैतिक दर्शनशास्त्र, and argued that the Declaration is a बयान of principles through which the United States Constitution चाहिए be interpreted.
It रै प्रेरित work लिये the अधिकारों of अधिकारहीन people throughout the संसार.

a region is arid when it is characterized by a कठोर कमी of available जल, to the extent of hindering or preventing the विकास and विकास of संयंत्र and एनिमल life.
Environments विषय to arid climates tend to lack वनस्पति and are called xeric or desertic.
सबसे `` arid '' climates घेर the equator ; these स्थान include सबसे of अफ़्रीकी और भाग of दक्षिण America और Central अमेरिका.
कर्कट ( ♋ ) is an astrological चिह्न, जिससे is संबद्ध with the नक्षत्र कर्कट.
It spans the 90-120th degree of the zodiac, between 90 और 125.25 उपाधि of celestial longitude, जिससे the सूर्य transits this area on औसत between June 22 to July 22 प्रत्येक साल.
और अंतर्गत the sidereal zodiac, it is फिलहाल इससे जुलाई 21 to अगस्त 9.
the संयुक्त राज्य अध्यक्षीय चुनाव of 1960 was the 44th quadrennial अध्यक्षीय election, आयोजित on मंगलवार, नवम्बर 8, 1960.
the Republican पार्टी nominated लाज़िम vice-president रिचर्ड Nixon, जबकि the Democratic Party nominated जॉन F. कैनेडी, सीनेटर इससे Massachusetts.
the incumbent President, रिपब्लिकन ड्वाइट D. आइज़नहावर, थी not योग्य लिये re-election after सेवारत the maximum दो शर्तें अनुमत by the Twenty-second amendment.
Kennedy थी निर्वाचित साथ a सीसे of 112,827 मत, or 0.17 % of the लोकप्रिय vote, giving him a victory of 303 to 219 in the Electoral कॉलेज, the closest चूंकि 1916.
This was the पहला election in which all पचास of the वर्तमान संयुक्त राज्य participated.
a number of factors explain क्यों the election थी so close.
कैनेडी gained चूंकि वहीँ थी an economic मंदी which hurt the incumbent Republican, और he था the लाभ of 17 लाख अधिक registered डेमोक्रेट than republicans.
furthermore, the new मत कि Kennedy gained among Catholics almost neutralized the नई votes निक्सन gained among Protestants.
Kennedy 's campaigning कौशल decisively outmatched निक्सन 's.
In the समाप्त, निक्सन 's emphasis on उसके अनुभव carried छोटी weight, and he wasted energy by campaigning in सब 50 राज्य बजाय of concentrating on the झूले राज्य.
Kennedy प्रयुक्त उसके large, well-funded अभियान संगठन to win the नामांकन, सुरक्षित endorsements, and, with the सहायता of the last of the big-city bosses, to मिलेंगी out the vote in the big cities.

The यूएसए patriot अधिनियम of 2001 is an अधिनियम of the U.S. कॉंग्रेस that थी signed into law by अध्यक्ष George W. बुश on अक्तूबर 26, 2001.
the शीर्षक of the act is a ten अक्षर एक्रोनिम ( यूएसए PATRIOT ) that stands लिये Uniting ( and ) strengthening America ( by ) providing उचित टूल्स Required ( to ) Intercept ( और ) obstruct आतंक Act of 2001.
The act, as a जवाब to the आतंकवादी हमले of सितंबर 11th, significantly घटाया प्रतिबंध in law enforcement agencies ' महफ़िल of प्रज्ञा भीतर the United राज्य ; expanded the Secretary of the treasury’s authority to विनियमित financial ट्रांजेक्शन, विशेषकर those involving विदेशी individuals और entities ; and broadened the discretion of विधि enforcement and आव्रजन अधिकारियों in निमाड़ और deporting immigrants suspected of terrorism-related acts.
The act also expanded the definition of आतंक to include domestic आतंक, यूँ enlarging the क्रमांक of क्रियाएँ to जिससे the USA PATRIOT Act’s expanded law enforcement शक्तियां can be लागू.
on may 26, 2011, अध्यक्ष बराक ओबामा प्रयुक्त an autopen to चिह्न the patriot sunsets Extension अधिनियम of 2011, a four-year extension of three कुंजी provisions in the यूएसए patriot Act while he was in फ़्रांस : roving wiretaps, खोज of कारोबार रिकॉर्ड ( the `` library records प्रावधान `` ), and conducting निगरानी of `` लोन भेड़ियों '' — individuals suspected of terrorist-related activities not linked to आतंकवादी समूह.
रिपब्लिकन leaders questioned if the उपयोग of the autopen मिले the constitutional आवश्यकताएँ for signing a विधेयक into law.

Transcendental जंगली जई : a अध्याय इससे an Unwritten रोमांस is a गद्य satire written by Louisa may Alcott, about उसके परिवार 's भागीदारी साथ the Transcendentalist community fruitlands in the जल्दी 1840s.
The कार्य थी पहला published in a नई York समाचारपत्र in 1873, और reprinted in 1874, 1876, और 1915 और after.

Her पिता Amos bronson Alcott is `` Abel मेमने, '' जबकि उसके partner and community co-founder चार्ल्स Lane is `` timon शेर ; '' Abigail May Alcott, Louisa 's माँ and Bronson 's बीवी, is `` सिस्टर Hope. ''
alcott depicts her पिता as वर्चस्व by उसके अधिक forceful partner, and both मेन as लापरवाह और अव्यवहारिक dreamers.
The men of the community spend their समय in pointless debates जबकि सिस्टर आशा works from भोर to dusk to maintain their अस्तित्व.
a संकट arises at harvest समय, when the grain crop is threatened by an approaching तूफ़ान.
In alcott 's शब्द, `` परिचय the समय the अनाज was ready to house, some कॉल of the Oversoul wafted all the मेन दूर. ''
Sister Hope organizes the तभी उपलब्धियाँ सहायता, तीन छोटी girls और a लड़के, and manages to सहेजें the crop.

Timon शेर and उसके son abscond to join the Shakers — हालांकि timon is unhappy to सीख कि जीवन among उन्हें is `` सब कार्य और no खेल. ''

alcott 's दृश्य of पुरूष arrogance and मादा शोषण in this piece is paralleled in her novel, published in the वही year as `` Transcendental जंगली Oats. ''

माउंट of the Holy क्रॉस is the northernmost 14,000-foot mountain in the Sawatch दायरा, भाग of the रॉकी Mountains in Colorado.
it is स्तिथ in the पावन Cross wilderness near the भुत कस्बा of Holy क्रॉस नगर and in त्रिभुज काउंटी.
it was नामित लिये the distinctive cross-shaped snowfield on the पूर्वोत्तर फेस.
अंतर्गत यूएसडीए वन Service administration, the mountain थी proclaimed `` पावन क्रॉस नेशनल Monument '' by हर्बर्ट हूवर on may 11, 1929.
The स्मारक was transferred to the नेशनल Park सेवा in 1933.
in 1950, it थी लौटे to the Forest सेवा और खोया its नेशनल स्मारक status—the क्रमांक of विज़िटर to the mountain and the आसपास `` pilgrim 's हट '' had waned, and the व्यय of full-time स्टाफ could नहीं be justified.
इस पहाड़ रै महरूम the subject of चित्रकार, फ़ोटोग्राफ़र and भी a कविता by Henry Wadsworth लांगफेलो, ( the Cross of हिम ).
the पहला सरेआम available फोटोग्राफ थी प्रकाशित in National Geographic magazine.
Thomas मोरान चित्रित the पहाड़ in an आयल painting, which now is भाग of the संग्रहण of the संग्रहालय of the American वेस्ट, भाग of the Autry National Center in लॉस Angeles, कैलिफ़ोर्निया.

Holy क्रॉस can be climbed by at तनिक चार different रूट, साथ the easiest और सबसे आम route होने the उत्तर Ridge, जिससे involves of vertical gain over और is rated YDS Class 2 लिये moderate scrambling.
The Cross couloir रूट फ़ॉर्म the vertical portion of the प्रसिद्ध cross feature, और provides an advanced हिम चढ़ाई or extreme स्की descent.
माउंट of the पावन Cross has a इतिहास of endangering the जीवनदान of अनेक hikers.
Primarily, the hikers जो require rescue are unfamiliar with the risks of प्रवेश wilderness areas और do not लाओ adequate उपकरण and आपूर्तियाँ to respond to emergency शर्तें.

the जीएसएम लोगो is used to identify संगत handsets और उपकरण
GSM ( Global प्रणाली for मोबाईल Communications, originally ' ), is a मानक नियत developed by the European दूरसंचार Standards संस्थान ( etsi ) to describe प्रोटोकॉल for second पीढी ( 2g ) डिजिटल सेल्यूलर networks प्रयुक्त by mobile phones.
it became the de facto वैश्विक मानक लिये मोबाईल communications with over 80 % market share.
The जीएसएम मानक was developed as a बदलना लिये पहला पीढी ( 1g ) एनालॉग cellular networks, and originally described a डिजिटल, circuit switched संजाल अनुकूलित for पूरा duplex voice telephony.
इस was expanded over time to include आंकड़ा संचार, पहला by सर्किट switched transport, then packet आंकड़ा हस्तांतरण via gprs ( सामान्य Packet Radio सेवाएं ) और किनारे ( उन्नत आंकड़ा दरों for GSM Evolution or EGPRS ).
Further improvements यहूद बना जब the 3GPP विकसित तीसरा पीढी ( 3g ) umts मानकों followed by fourth पीढी ( 4g ) lte Advanced मानकों.
`` जीएसएम '' is a trademark स्वामित्व by the जीएसएम Association.
अध्यक्ष Franklin D. रूज़वेल्ट लक्षण the Lend-Lease bill to give सहायता to ब्रिटेन और चीन ( 1941 )
the Lend पट्टे act was an अधिनियम where the संयुक्त राज्य had supported इसके allies.
lend-lease ( ) was the विधि that प्रारंभ a कार्यक्रम अंतर्गत which the संयुक्त राज्य of America supplied the संयुक्त किंगडम, the USSR, Republic of China, Free France, and other अलाइड nations साथ materiel between 1941 और 1945.
it was signed into विधि on March 11, 1941, a year and a half बाद the outbreak of World युद्ध II in Europe in September 1939.
This was नौ महीने पहले the u.S. डाला the युद्ध in December 1941.
formally titled an अधिनियम to further प्रचार the रक्षा of the United राज्य, the अधिनियम effectively ended the संयुक्त राज्य ' pretense of neutrality.
A कुल of $ 50.1 अरब ( समतुल्य to $ आज ) लायक of आपूर्तियाँ were shipped : $ 31.4 अरब to ब्रिटेन, $ 11.3 billion to the Soviet संघ, $ 3.2 अरब to फ़्रांस, $ 1.6 billion to चीन, and छोटी sums to अन्य Allies.
रिवर्स lend-lease comprised services ऐसे as rent on air bases कि went to the U.S., और totaled $ 7.8 अरब ; of this, $ 6.8 billion आए इससे the अंग्रेजों and the राष्ट्रमंडल.
The terms of the अनुबंध provided that the materiel थी to be प्रयुक्त जबतक time लिये उनके वापसी or विनाश.
Supplies after the termination date were sold to Britain at a विशाल छूट लिये £1.075 billion using long-term लोन इससे the संयुक्त States.
कनाडा संचालित a समान कार्यक्रम कि भेजा $ 4.7 billion in आपूर्तियाँ to the संयुक्त किंगडम और the Soviet Union.
the संयुक्त राज्य किया नहीं चार्ज लिये सहायता supplied अंतर्गत this legislation.
इस program was a निर्णायक कदम away इससे non-interventionist नीति, which था वर्चस्व संयुक्त राज्य foreign relations चूंकि the समाप्त of World युद्ध i, towards अंतरराष्ट्रीय भागीदारी.
The जेरूसलम artichoke ( helianthus tuberosus ), also पुकारा sunroot, sunchoke, earth apple or topinambour, is a प्रजाति of sunflower देशी to पूर्वी North America, और found from eastern Canada और maine वेस्ट to North डकोटा, and south to उत्तरी फ्लोरिडा और Texas.
It is भी cultivated widely आरपार the शीतोष्ण मण्डल लिये इसके tuber, जिससे is प्रयुक्त as a रूट सब्ज़ी.

Stonehenge is a prehistoric स्मारक in विल्टशायर, England, परिचय वेस्ट of Amesbury और उत्तर of salisbury.
एक of the सबसे famous sites in the world, Stonehenge is the remains of a ring of standing पत्थरों नियत भीतर earthworks.
It is in the middle of the सबसे dense complex of Neolithic और Bronze आयु स्मारक in इंग्लैण्ड, including अनेक सौ दफ़न mounds.
archaeologists मानना it थी built anywhere from 3000 BC to 2000 BC.
Radiocarbon dating in 2008 सुझाया कि the पहला पत्थरों were raised between 2400 and 2200 BC, whilst another सिद्धान्त suggests that bluestones may have महरूम उठाया at the site as early as 3000 bc.
the surrounding गोलाकार धरती बैंको and ditch, which constitute the earliest phase of the स्मारक, have महरूम dated to about 3100 BC.
the साईट और इसके परिवेश were added to the UNESCO 's सूची of संसार विरासत साइट in 1986 in a co-listing with avebury Henge.
It is a national legally protected अनुसूचित Ancient Monument.
stonehenge is स्वामित्व by the क्राउन और managed by English Heritage, जबकि the surrounding जमीन is owned by the नेशनल विश्वास.
पुरातत्व प्रमाण मिला by the Stonehenge riverside Project in 2008 indicates that stonehenge could have been a burial ground from its earliest beginnings.
the डेटिंग of cremated remains मिला on the site indicate that जमा contain human अस्थि from as जल्दी as 3000 bc, when the खाई and बैंको यहूद first dug.
Such जमा जारी at Stonehenge लिये at तनिक another 500 सालो.

Held प्रत्येक अप्रैल, the महिलाओं 's चैंपियनशिप was उदघाटन in the 1981–82 ऋतु.
The NCAA टूर्नामेंट थी preceded by the AIAW महिलाओं 's Basketball टूर्नामेंट, जिससे थी held annually from 1972 to 1982.
बास्केट थी एक of twelve महिलाओं 's sports added to the NCAA championship कार्यक्रम लिये the 1981-82 school साल, as the ncaa सगाई in बैटल साथ the संघ for intercollegiate Athletics लिये महिलाओं for sole शासन of महिलाओं 's कॉलेजिएट खेल.
The AIAW जारी to conduct इसके स्थापित चैंपियनशिप कार्यक्रम in the same बारह ( और अन्य ) खेल ; however, बाद a year of डुअल महिलाओं 's championships, the ncaa prevailed, जबकि the AIAW disbanded.
उपस्थिति और interest in the महिलाओं 's प्रभाग i चैंपियनशिप have grown over the सालो, विशेषकर चूंकि 2003, जब the फाइनल चैंपियनशिप खेल थी moved to the मंगलवार following the Monday men 's चैंपियनशिप खेल.
the महिलाओं 's चैंपियनशिप खेल is now the final overall game of the college बास्केट season.
पहले कि, the Women 's फाइनल चार थी प्रायः played on the शुक्रवार पहले the मेन 's फाइनल चार or the घंटों पहले the मेन played on the फाइनल शनिवार of the tournament.
the फाइनल थी usually निभाई the संडे दोपहर following the मेन 's फाइनल चार.
the टूर्नामेंट कोष्ठक is बना up of champions इससे प्रत्येक Division I सम्मेलन, जिससे receive automatic bids.
the बाकी स्लॉट हैं at-large bids, with टीमों chosen by an ncaa चयन कमेटी.
the चयन प्रक्रम and टूर्नामेंट seedings are based on several कारकों, including टोली rankings, win-loss records and दरजा प्रतिशत अनुक्रमणिका ( rpi ) data.
नापसंद the men 's tournament, वहीँ हैं तभी 32 at-large bids ( as of the next टूर्नामेंट in 2014 ), and no play-in खेल.
the women 's टूर्नामेंट, like the मेन 's, is staged in a सिंगल विलोपन स्वरूप, और is भाग of the मीडिया और पब्लिक frenzy ज्ञात colloquially as March Madness or The बिग नृत्य.
सब 63 games have been ब्रॉडकास्ट on television चूंकि 2003 on ईएसपीएन and ESPN2.
समान to the pre-2011 मेन 's टूर्नामेंट coverage on CBS, लोकल टीमों are shown on each चैनल when available, with `` whip-around '' coverage designed to showcase the सबसे प्रतिस्पर्धी contests in the rest of the देश.
the Rosetta स्टोन in the British संग्रहालय
the rosetta स्टोन is an प्राचीन Egyptian granodiorite stele inscribed साथ a डिक्री जारी at मेम्फिस in 196 bc on behalf of किंग Ptolemy V.
the डिक्री appears in तीन scripts : the upper टेक्स्ट is Ancient Egyptian चित्रलिपि, the मध्य portion demotic स्क्रिप्ट, और the न्यूनतम Ancient यूनानी.
क्युकी it presents essentially the same टेक्स्ट in all तीन स्क्रिप्ट ( साथ some minor मतभेद between उन्हें ), it provided the key to the आधुनिक समझना of मिश्र चित्रलिपि.
Originally displayed भीतर a टेम्पल, the stone थी संभवतः moved दौरान the early Christian or मध्यकालीन period और eventually प्रयुक्त as building material in the निर्माण of Fort जुलिएन near the कस्बा of रशीद ( Rosetta ) in the Nile Delta.
it was rediscovered वहीँ in 1799 by a soldier, pierre-françois bouchard, of the French expedition to मिश्र.
As the पहला प्राचीन मिश्र दुभाषिया टेक्स्ट बरामद in modern times, the Rosetta Stone aroused फैली पब्लिक ब्याज साथ इसके संभावित to decipher this hitherto untranslated प्राचीन language.
Lithographic नक़ल and प्लास्टर casts began circulating among यूरोपीय संग्रहालय और scholars.
Meanwhile, British troops defeated the फ्रेंच in मिश्र in 1801, और the original स्टोन came into British possession अंतर्गत the Capitulation of एलेक्जेंड्रिया.
transported to London, it has been on public प्रदर्शक at the अंग्रेजों संग्रहालय चूंकि 1802.
It is the most-visited ऑब्जेक्ट in the British Museum.
कभी चूंकि its rediscovery, the स्टोन रै been the फ़ोकस of राष्ट्रवादी rivalries, including इसके ट्रांसफ़र from फ्रेंच to British कब्ज़ा दौरान the napoleonic युद्धों, a long-running dispute over the सापेक्ष मान of Young 's and Champollion 's contributions to the decipherment, and चूंकि 2003, मांगे लिये the stone 's वापसी to मिश्र.
Study of the decree was already अंतर्गत way as the पहला पूरा अनुवाद of the Greek टेक्स्ट appeared in 1803.
it was 20 years, however, पहले the transliteration of the Egyptian स्क्रिप्ट थी announced by jean-françois champollion in पेरिस in 1822 ; it took longer still before विद्वानों यहूद समर्थ to read Ancient Egyptian inscriptions and literature confidently.
प्रमुख अग्रिम in the decoding यहूद : मान्यता कि the स्टोन offered तीन संस्करण of the वही टेक्स्ट ( 1799 ) ; कि the demotic टेक्स्ट used ध्वन्यात्मक characters to spell foreign names ( 1802 ) ; कि the hieroglyphic text did so as well, और had pervasive similarities to the demotic ( थामस Young, 1814 ) ; and that, in जोड to होने used लिये foreign names, ध्वन्यात्मक characters were भी प्रयुक्त to spell native मिश्र words ( champollion, 1822–1824 ).
दो अन्य fragmentary copies of the वही decree यहूद discovered बाद, and several similar Egyptian दुभाषिया or trilingual inscriptions हैं अभी ज्ञात, सहित दो slightly earlier Ptolemaic डिक्री ( the डिक्री of canopus in 238 bc, और the मेम्फिस decree of टॉलेमी iv, ca. 218 bc ).
the Rosetta Stone is इसलिए no longer unique, लकिन it थी the अनिवार्य कुंजी to modern understanding of Ancient Egyptian साहित्य और civilization.
The पद Rosetta Stone is अभी used in other contexts as the name लिये the essential सुराग to a new field of ज्ञान.
ज़हर डार्ट मेंढक ( भी dart-poison frog, poison मेंढक or formerly ज़हर तीर frog ) is the आम name of a समूह of मेंढक in the परिवार dendrobatidae जिससे हैं native to Central and South अमेरिका.
ये species हैं diurnal और often have brightly colored लाशें.
हालांकि सब wild dendrobatids are at तनिक somewhat विषाक्त, स्तर of toxicity vary considerably from एक species to the next and इससे one जनसांख्यिकी to another.
अनेक प्रजाति हैं threatened.
ये amphibians हैं प्रायः पुकारा `` डार्ट मेंढक '' due to the amerindians ' स्वदेशी use of उनके to ज़हर the tips of blowdarts.
however, of over 175 species, तभी four have been प्रलेखित as होने प्रयुक्त for this purpose ( curare plants हैं more commonly प्रयुक्त ), सब of जिससे आइये इससे the phyllobates genus, which is characterized by the अपेक्षाकृत विशाल आकार and high स्तर of toxicity of इसके सदस्यों.
cajeta is a Mexican confection of thickened syrup प्रायः made of sweetened caramelised मिल्क.
according to शेफ़ रिक Bayless, the name लिये cajeta आए from the Spanish phrase al punto de cajeta, जिससे अर्थात् `` a liquid thickened to the point at जिससे a spoon drawn through the द्रव reveals the bottom of the pot in जिससे it is होने cooked ''.
Another परिकल्पना is कि it takes its name इससे the small लकड़ी boxes in जिससे it was traditionally packed.
मैक्सिकन cajeta is माना a specialty of the नगर of celaya in the state of Guanajuato, हालांकि it is भी उत्पादित साथ the परंपरागत विधि in अनेक towns of the राज्य of jalisco, such as mazamitla, Sayula, and atotonilco el आल्टो.
cajeta is बना by simmering बकरी 's मिल्क, or occasionally a sweetened द्रव, stirring अक्सर, until it becomes very viscous due to वाष्पीकरण of water, और caramelized.
जबकि बकरी milk is the most usual आधार, अन्य liquids or रस may be प्रयुक्त.
In celaya, और आखिरकार the rest of Mexico, the confection of half बकरी 's मिल्क और हाफ गाय 's मिल्क became known by the name cajeta, लकिन elsewhere, the मिल्क कैंडी became ज्ञात as leche quemada, dulce de leche, etc.
It रै cousins in the अनेक भारतीय milk-based sweets like प्रभा और the मिल्क फ़ज burfi, और in the opera fudge of the u.S. Cajeta is खाया on इसके own as a sweet, as a spread or भरना for breads and pastries, ऐसे as churros, और as a टॉपिंग लिये बर्फ cream.
Certain liquors हैं added to खास recipes पुकारा cajeta envinada.
in addition, cajeta envinada especial is समृद्ध साथ किशमिश, बादाम, pecans or nuts.
प्रायः it is प्रयुक्त as a टॉपिंग लिये crêpes, as a मीठी सॉस boiled और softened bas साथ milk to soak the crepes, resulting in a tasty मिठाई.
In Mexico अनेक ब्रांड्स मेक cajeta लकिन the most common ब्रांड is Coronado.
it is भी बहुत आम to प्लेस cajeta between obleas to मेक a परंपरागत मैक्सिकन dessert.
प्रिंस विलियम, ड्यूक of कैम्ब्रिज ( William आर्थर फिलिप Louis ; born 21 June 1982 ), is the elder son of चार्ल्स, Prince of Wales, और Diana, राजकुमारी of वेल्स, and third-eldest पोता of महारानी एलिज़ाबेथ ii and Prince फिलिप, ड्यूक of एडिनबर्ग.
he is second in the line of उत्तराधिकार, पीछे his father, to the तख्तों of sixteen स्वतंत्र sovereign राज्य known as the राष्ट्रमंडल realms : the संयुक्त Kingdom, Canada, ऑस्ट्रेलिया, नई जीलैंड, Jamaica, Barbados, the बहामा, हरा, Papua नई गिनी, the Solomon आइलैंड्स, Tuvalu, संत लूसिया, संत विंसेंट and the grenadines, Belize, अण्टीगुआ और Barbuda, और Saint किट्स and Nevis.
प्रिंस विलियम थी educated at चार schools in the United किंगडम और obtained a degree इससे the विश्वविद्यालयों of st एंड्रयूज.
he खर्च भाग of a gap साल in चिली, बेलीज़, Tanzania, और कीनिया जहाँ he has जिया and holidayed अनेक times.
Prince विलियम रै also लिया kiswahili अध्ययन at विश्वविद्यालयों in Kenya और Tanzania.
he was commissioned as a Lieutenant in the ब्लूज़ और रॉयल्स Regiment of the household प्यादे —serving साथ उसके bhai प्रिंस हैरी —and, two years later, अर्जित उसके wings by completing पायलट training at royal एयर Force College cranwell.
in 2009, he transferred to the royal एयर फ़ोर्स, was promoted to उड़ान लेफ्टिनेंट और underwent helicopter उड़ती प्रशिक्षण in order to become a full-time pilot साथ the Search and बचाव फ़ोर्स.
In 2010, he समाप्त his सामान्य और special-to-type helicopter प्रशिक्षण और went on to raf घाटी on No. 22 स्क्वाड्रन performing co-pilot कर्तव्य on board a Sea King search and बचाव helicopter.
प्रिंस विलियम married उसके longtime गर्लफ्रेंड, Catherine मिडलटन, on 29 April 2011 at Westminster ऐबी.
Hours prior to his विवाह, प्रिंस विलियम थी created ड्यूक of कैम्ब्रिज, अर्ल of Strathearn, और सामन्त carrickfergus.
माली is a multilingual देश.
the भाषाएं बोला there प्रतिबिंबित प्राचीन settlement पैटर्न, migrations, and इसके long इतिहास.
ऍथनोलॉग रिश्तो 50 भाषाएं.
of these, फ्रेंच is the आधिकारिक भाषा और bambara is the most widely spoken.

9 – 12 फ़रवरी ( वियतनाम )
रोजर्स Building, the headquarters of Rogers संचार
रोजर्स संचार inc. is a diversified public Canadian संचार and media कम्पनी.
it is particularly in the field of बेतार communications, cable television, telephone, and Internet connectivity साथ significant अतिरिक्त दूरसंचार और द्रव्यमान media assets.
the कम्पनी is headquartered in the Rogers Building in टोरंटो, Ontario.
the कम्पनी claims the विरासत of the रोजर्स Vacuum ट्यूब Company, founded in 1925 by Edward रोजर्स, which प्रारंभ the cfrb radio स्टेशन in Toronto, जिससे थी later acquired by बाहर interests.
the present enterprise तिथियाँ to 1960, जब रोजर्स ' son, टेड Rogers, founded रोजर्स Radio प्रसारण ltd.
That company acquired chfi कि year, as खूब as Aldred-Rogers प्रसारण, a partnership साथ जोएल Aldred which helped launch cfto in 1961.
Rogers बाद bought आउट aldred और प्रारंभ the current केबल और बेतार परिचालन, known as रोजर्स Cablesystems Ltd.
The मुख्य प्रतिस्पर्धी to the कम्पनी is घंटी कनाडा, which रै a similarly extensive portfolio of radio और television media एसेट, as खूब as बेतार, टेलीविज़न वितरण, और telephone services, विशेषकर in Eastern और सेंट्रल कनाडा ; the दो कंपनियाँ हैं often देखी as having a द्वयाधिकार on संचार सेवाएं in उनके regions.
however, the company भी competes nationally साथ telus for बेतार services, and primarily indirectly साथ Shaw संचार for टेलीविज़न service.
The कम्पनी also competes with a number of other मीडिया कंपनियाँ in the broadcasting उद्योग.
The अंतरजाल is a वैश्विक प्रणाली of interconnected कंप्यूटर संजाल कि उपयोग the standard अंतरजाल प्रोटोकॉल सुइट ( TCP/IP ) to serve अरबों of users worldwide.
It is a संजाल of networks that consists of millions of निजी, पब्लिक, अकादमिक, कारोबार, और government संजाल, of local to global scope, कि are linked by a broad array of इलेक्ट्रॉनिक, wireless और optical networking technologies.
the अंतरजाल carries an extensive दायरा of सूचना resources and सेवाएं, ऐसे as the inter-linked hypertext documents of the World Wide Web ( www ) और the अवसंरचना to support ईमेल.
सबसे परंपरागत communications media सहित telephone, म्यूज़िक, film, और टेलीविज़न are being reshaped or redefined by the अंतरजाल, giving जनम to नई सेवाएं ऐसे as voice over Internet Protocol ( VoIP ) और Internet प्रोटोकॉल टेलीविज़न ( iptv ).
Newspaper, किताब और अन्य print publishing हैं adapting to Web साईट प्रौद्योगिकी, or हैं reshaped into blogging और web फ़ीड्स.
the Internet has enabled and accelerated नई forms of इंसान interactions through instant messaging, Internet forums, और सोशल नेटवर्किंग.
ऑनलाइन खरीदारी रै boomed both for प्रमुख खुदरा outlets और छोटी शिल्पकार और traders.
Business-to-business and वित्तीय सेवाएं on the अंतरजाल affect सप्लाई chains आरपार संपूर्ण उद्योग.
the origins of the अंतरजाल reach back to शोध commissioned by the संयुक्त राज्य सरकारी in the 1960s to निर्माण robust, fault-tolerant communication via कंप्यूटर networks.
The funding of a नई U.S. रीढ़ by the नेशनल Science Foundation in the 1980s, as खूब as निजी funding for अन्य commercial backbones, led to विश्वव्यापी participation in the विकास of नई नेटवर्किंग technologies, और the विलय of many संजाल.
the व्यावसायीकरण of कया थी by the 1990s an अंतरराष्ट्रीय संजाल resulted in इसके popularization और incorporation into virtually प्रत्येक पहलू of आधुनिक human जीवन.
, more than 2.4 अरब people—over a तीसरा of the संसार 's इंसान जनसांख्यिकी —have प्रयुक्त the सेवाएं of the Internet ; approximately 100 टाइम्स more लोगों than यहूद using it in 1995, जब it थी ज़्यादातर प्रयुक्त by tech-savvy मध्य and अपर क्लास लोगों in the संयुक्त राज्य और several अन्य देशों.
the अंतरजाल has no centralized governance in either technological क्रियान्वयन or नीतियों लिये अभिगम और उपयोग ; each constituent network सेट its अपना policies.
Only the overreaching परिभाषाएं of the two प्रिंसिपल नाम स्पेसेस in the अंतरजाल, the अंतरजाल Protocol address space and the Domain Name प्रणाली, हैं निर्देशित by a maintainer संगठन, the अंतरजाल Corporation लिये Assigned names और Numbers ( icann ).
the technical underpinning and मानकीकरण of the कोर प्रोटोकॉल ( IPv4 और IPv6 ) is an activity of the अंतरजाल अभियान्त्रिकी Task फ़ोर्स ( ietf ), a non-profit संगठन of loosely संबद्ध अंतरराष्ट्रीय भागीदार that anyone may associate साथ by contributing तकनीकी विशेषज्ञता.
The 2006 Winter ओलंपिक, officially known as the XX ओलम्पिक Winter खेल, थी a शीत multi-sport इवेंट जिससे was मनाये in Turin, इटली इससे फ़रवरी 10, 2006, through February 26, 2006.
This marked the second समय इटली hosted the ओलम्पिक Winter Games, the पहला होने the सात Olympic Winter Games in cortina d'Ampezzo in 1956.
इटली भी hosted the Games of the XVII ओलंपियाड in रोम in 1960.
Turin थी selected as the host नगर for the 2006 खेल in 1999.
The आधिकारिक logo प्रदर्शित the name `` टोरिनो '', the इतालवी नाम of the नगर ; the city is ज्ञात as `` टोरीनो '' in दोनो अंग्रेज़ी और the local परंपरागत भाषा, Piedmontese.
the ओलम्पिक mascots of Torino 2006 were Neve ( `` हिम '' in Italian ), a female स्नोबॉल, and Gliz, a पुरूष ice घन.
the आधिकारिक motto of the xx Olympic शीत खेल was `` जुनून जीवनदान यहाँ ''.
`` Help ! '' is a सोंग by the बीटल्स कि परोसा as the शीर्षक song लिये दोनो the 1965 film और इसके soundtrack एल्बम.

Kennewick is a नगर in Benton County in the southeastern part of the U.S. राज्य of वॉशिंगटन, निकट the hanford nuclear साईट.

the prothrombin समय ( pt ) और its निकला measures of prothrombin अनुपात ( pr ) और international सामान्यीकृत ratio ( INR ) हैं measures of the extrinsic pathway of coagulation.
इस परीक्षण is भी called `` protime inr '' and `` PT/INR ''.
वे हैं used to determine the clotting tendency of blood, in the माप of warfarin dosage, जिगर क्षति, और विटामिन K status.
pt उपायों कारकों i ( fibrinogen ), II ( prothrombin ), V, सात, और x.
It is प्रयुक्त in conjunction साथ the activated partial thromboplastin time ( aPTT ) which measures the मूलभूत pathway.

cross-cultural मनोविज्ञान is the वैज्ञानिक study of इंसान behavior और दिमागी processes, including दोनो their variability और invariance, अंतर्गत विविध cultural शर्तें.
through expanding research methodologies to recognize cultural variance in behavior, language, और meaning it seeks to extend और develop psychology.
Since मनोविज्ञान as an academic अनुशासन was developed largely in उत्तर America, कुछ psychologists became चिंतित that constructs स्वीकृत as सार्वभौमिक यहूद not as invariant as previously assumed, especially since many कोशिशें to replicate notable प्रयोग in अन्य संस्कृतियों था varying कामयाबी.
चूंकि वहीँ हैं सवाल as to whether theories dealing साथ सेंट्रल themes, ऐसे as affect, संज्ञान, conceptions of the self, और issues ऐसे as psychopathology, anxiety, और अवसाद, may कमी बाह्य वैध when `` exported '' to other cultural contexts, cross-cultural psychology re-examines उन्हें using methodologies designed to फ़ैक्टर in cultural differences so as to खाता for सांस्कृतिक variance.
हालांकि some critics have pointed to methodological flaws in cross-cultural psychological research and अर्जी कि गंभीर shortcomings in the theoretical और methodological bases प्रयुक्त impede बल्कि than सहायता the scientific ढूंढें लिये universal सिद्धान्त in psychology, cross-cultural psychologists are turning अधिक to the study of कैसा differences ( variance ) occur, बल्कि than searching लिये universals in the स्टाइल of भौतिकी or chemistry.
In 1972 the International संघ of cross-cultural Psychology ( IACCP ) थी स्थापित.
इस branch of मनोविज्ञान रै जारी to expand as वहीँ रै महरूम an increasing लोकप्रियता of incorporating संस्कृति और विविधता into अध्ययन.
Cross-cultural psychology is differentiated इससे Cultural मनोविज्ञान.
The latter is the branch of psychology that holds कि इंसान बर्ताव is significantly influenced by सांस्कृतिक मतभेद, अर्थ that मनोवैज्ञानिक phenomena can तभी be compared साथ प्रत्येक other across cultures to a बहुत सीमित extent.
in कंट्रास्ट, cross-cultural मनोविज्ञान includes a ढूंढें for possible universals in behavior and दिमागी प्रक्रियाओं.
Walter J. lonner, लिखने लिये नजर on Psi ची, रै stated कि `` cross-cultural psychology can be विचार of as a प्रकार शोध methodology, बल्कि than an entirely पृथक field within psychology ( 2000 ). ''

H.264/MPEG-4 Part 10 or avc ( उन्नत वीडियो Coding ) is a मानक for video संपीडन, और is फिलहाल one of the सबसे commonly used स्वरुप for the recording, compression, और distribution of ऊँची परिभाषा वीडियो.
The फाइनल drafting कार्य on the first संस्करण of the standard थी समाप्त in May 2003.
H.264/MPEG-4 AVC is a block-oriented motion-compensation -आधारd कोडेक मानक developed by the ITU-T Video कोडिंग Experts समूह ( VCEG ) साथ साथ the ISO/IEC jtc1 Moving Picture Experts Group ( MPEG ).
the प्रोजेक्ट साझेदारी प्रयत्न is known as the संयुक्त वीडियो टोली ( JVT ).
The itu-t h.264 मानक और the iso/iec mpeg-4 AVC मानक ( formally, ISO/IEC 14496-10 – MPEG-4 Part 10, Advanced वीडियो Coding ) हैं jointly कायम so that they have एकसमान technical सामग्री.
H.264 is शायद best ज्ञात as होने एक of the कोडेक मानकों लिये blu-ray discs ; सब blu-ray डिस्क players must be able to decode h.264.
It is भी widely प्रयुक्त by स्ट्रीमिंग internet स्त्रोत, ऐसे as वीडियो इससे Vimeo, youtube, और the itunes स्टोर, वेब तन्त्र ऐसे as the Adobe Flash खिलाड़ी और microsoft Silverlight, and also विभिन्न hdtv broadcasts over terrestrial ( ATSC, isdb-t, dvb-t or dvb-t2 ), केबल ( dvb-c ) and उपग्रह ( dvb-s और DVB-S2 ).
non-binding arbitration is a प्रकार of मध्यस्थता in जिससे the arbitrator makes a determination of the rights of the पार्टियों to the dispute, लकिन इस determination is not binding upon उन्हें, और no enforceable मध्यस्थता award is issued.
the `` award '' is in प्रभाव an सलाहकार राय of the arbitrator 's दृश्य of the respective merits of the पार्टियों मामले.
non-binding मध्यस्थता is used in कनेक्शन साथ attempts to reach a negotiated settlement.
the भूमिका of an arbitrator in non-binding मध्यस्थता is, on the सतह, similar to कि of a मध्यस्थ in a mediation.
however, the प्रिंसिपल भेद is कि whereas a mediator होगा कोशिश to help the पार्टियों ढूँढें a middle मैदान to compromise at, the arbitrator remains totally removed from the उपनिवेश प्रक्रम and होगा तभी दे a determination of liability और, if उचित, an indication of the quantum of क्षतिपूर्ति देय.
Subsequent to a non-binding arbitration, the parties remain फ़्री to pursue their दावा either through the courts, or by way of a बाइंडिंग मध्यस्थता, although in practice a उपनिवेश is the सबसे common निष्कर्ष.
the पुरस्कार और reasoning in a non-binding arbitration is लगभग invariably inadmissible in कोई subsequent action in the न्यायालयों or in another मध्यस्थता tribunal.
non-binding arbitration is utilised ज़्यादातर in the संयुक्त States और Canada.
it is largely unknown in Europe, हालांकि in the United किंगडम there is a अभ्यास of पार्टियों who are seeking a उपनिवेश to jointly instruct a महारानी 's counsel लिये an राय on the merits और संभावित quantum of a अर्जी, और then to negotiate on the basis of the views expressed in कि राय.
अगस्टाइन ज्वालामुखी is a लावा Dome जटिल on Augustine द्वीप in southwestern कुक Inlet in the kenai Peninsula Borough of southcentral coastal Alaska, दक्षिणपश्चिम of anchorage.

अगस्टाइन द्वीप रै a जमीन क्षेत्रफल of, while वेस्ट Island, just बंद अगस्टाइन 's western shores, रै.

अलास्का ( ) is a state in the संयुक्त States, situated in the northwest extremity of the North American महाद्वीप, साथ the अंतरराष्ट्रीय boundary साथ कनाडा to the east, the आर्कटिक समंदर to the उत्तर, और the प्रशांत Ocean to the वेस्ट और south, with रूस further वेस्ट आरपार the बेरिंग Strait.
Alaska is the largest state in the United States by क्षेत्रफल, the 4th तनिक populous और the तनिक densely populated of the 50 United States.
Approximately half of अलास्का 's 731,449 निवासियों सजीव भीतर the anchorage महानगर क्षेत्रफल.
अलास्का 's अर्थव्यवस्था is dominated by the आयल, natural गैस, and fishing उद्योग ; it रै ये संसाधन in प्रचुरता.
अलास्का थी खरीदा इससे Russia on कूच 30, 1867, लिये $ 7.2 लाख ( $ adjusted for महंगाई ) at लगभग two cents per एकड़ ( $ 4.74/km2 ).
the जमीन went through अनेक प्रशासनिक परिवर्तन before बनने an organized ( or incorporated ) territory on may 11, 1912, and the 49th state of the u.S. on जनवरी 3, 1959.
the नाम `` Alaska '' ( аляска ) थी already introduced in the Russian औपनिवेशिक काल, जब it was प्रयुक्त तभी लिये the प्रायद्वीप और is निकला इससे the aleut alaxsxaq, अर्थ `` the मेनलैंड '' or, more वस्तुतः, `` the object towards which the कार्रवाई of the sea is directed ''.
It is also known as Alyeska, the `` great जमीन '', an aleut word निकला from the same root.
नेल्सन Mandela महानगर University ( nmmu ) is a दक्षिण African tertiary education संस्था साथ its प्रमुख administration in the तटीय city of बंदरगाहों एलिज़ाबेथ.
A merging of three institutions founded nmmu in January 2005 लकिन its history तिथियाँ वापस to 1882 साथ the foundation of बंदरगाहों एलिज़ाबेथ आर्ट School.
the विश्वविद्यालयों draws अंतरराष्ट्रीय विद्यार्थी इससे सब over the world.
There are over 3000 अंतरराष्ट्रीय विद्यार्थी and शामिल students इससे the संयुक्त राज्य, फ़्रांस, चीन, जर्मनी, बेल्जियम, Denmark, Finland, Netherlands, Norway, स्वीडन, संयुक्त Kingdom और अनेक अन्य देशों.
nmmu is a व्यापक विश्वविद्यालयों offering पेशेवर और वोकेशनल प्रशिक्षण.
The विश्वविद्यालयों रै छह campuses - पाँच in बंदरगाहों Elizabeth और one in जार्ज.
