On the उत्पत्ति of प्रजाति, published on 24 November 1859, is a work of scientific literature by चार्ल्स Darwin which is considered to be the foundation of विकासवादी जीवविज्ञान.
इसके पूरा शीर्षक थी on the उत्पत्ति of प्रजाति by Means of प्राकृतिक चयन, or the संरक्षण of favoured दौड़ in the संघर्ष लिये Life.
For the छठे संस्करण of 1872, the छोटी शीर्षक was बदला to The उत्पत्ति of Species.
Darwin 's किताब introduced the वैज्ञानिक theory that populations evolve over the कोर्स of पीढियां through a process of natural चयन.
It प्रस्तुत a body of प्रमाण कि the diversity of जीवन arose by आम descent through a branching पैटर्न of एवोल्यूशन.
Darwin included प्रमाण कि he था gathered on the beagle expedition in the 1830s और उसके subsequent findings from शोध, पत्राचार, और experimentation.
Various evolutionary विचार had already महरूम प्रस्तावित to बताइये नई निष्कर्षों in जीवविज्ञान.
वहीँ was growing support for such ideas among dissident anatomists and the सामान्य पब्लिक, लकिन during the first हाफ of the 19th सदी the अंग्रेज़ी scientific स्थापना थी closely tied to the गिरिजाघर of इंग्लैण्ड, जबकि विज्ञान was part of natural theology.
Ideas परिचय the transmutation of प्रजाति were controversial as वे विरोधी with the beliefs कि species were अपरिवर्तनशील parts of a designed पदानुक्रम और that इंसानो यहूद अद्वितीय, unrelated to अन्य पशु.
the political और theological implications यहूद पडती debated, but transmutation थी not स्वीकृत by the scientific mainstream.
the किताब थी written लिये non-specialist पाठक and आकर्षित widespread ब्याज upon its प्रकाशन.
As Darwin was an प्रतिष्ठित वैज्ञानिक, उसके निष्कर्षों were taken seriously और the evidence he प्रस्तुत उत्पन्न वैज्ञानिक, philosophical, and धार्मिक चर्चा.
the बहस over the book contributed to the अभियान by T.H. Huxley and उसके fellow members of the x Club to secularise science by promoting वैज्ञानिक naturalism.
भीतर दो दशकों वहीँ थी widespread वैज्ञानिक अनुबंध that evolution, with a branching pattern of common descent, था occurred, लकिन वैज्ञानिकों were slow to दे प्राकृतिक चयन the significance कि Darwin thought appropriate.
दौरान the `` ग्रहण of डार्विनवाद `` from the 1880s to the 1930s, विभिन्न other mechanisms of evolution यहूद दिए अधिक क्रेडिट.
साथ the विकास of the आधुनिक evolutionary संश्लेषण in the 1930s and 1940s, Darwin 's concept of विकासवादी adaptation through प्राकृतिक selection became सेंट्रल to आधुनिक evolutionary सिद्धान्त, now the unifying concept of the जीवन sciences.
Charles डिलन `` Casey '' Stengel ( ; जुलाई 30, 1890 – सितंबर 29, 1975 ), nicknamed `` The बूढ़ा Perfessor '', थी an अमरीकी Major लीग Baseball outfielder and मैनेजर.
he was elected to the बेसबॉल Hall of Fame in.
स्टेंगल थी born in Kansas नगर, मिसौरी, और originally nicknamed `` डच '', a आम उपनाम at कि time लिये अमेरिकी of German ancestry.
After उसके major league करियर began, he acquired the nickname `` Casey '', which originally came from the आद्याक्षर of उसके hometown ( `` K. C. '' ), which evolved into `` केसी '', बहकावे by the चौड़ी popularity of the कविता केसी at the चमगादड़.
in the 1950s, sportswriters उतावले उसे साथ yet another nickname, `` the Old प्राध्यापक '' ( or `` Perfessor '' ), for his sharp wit और उसके ability to बात at length on anything बेसबॉल -related.
हालांकि उसके बेसबॉल career spanned a number of teams और शहरों, he is primarily associated साथ क्लब in नई यॉर्क नगर.
between playing and managing, he is the only man to have worn four of New यॉर्क 's प्रमुख लीग क्लब ' वर्दी.
He थी the पहला of चार मेन ( through the season ) to manage दोनो the नई यॉर्क Yankees और New यॉर्क Mets ; योगी berra, डलास ग्रीन, and Joe टोरेस हैं the अन्य.
जैसे Torre, he also managed the braves and the Dodgers.
He ended his बेसबॉल career as the beloved manager for the तब विस्तार नई York मेट्स, which जीती over the दिल of New यॉर्क partly due to the अद्वितीय अक्षर of उनके दिग्गज leader.
जून ( ) is the छठे month of the साल in the Julian और Gregorian calendars और एक of the four months with a लंबाई of 30 दिनों.
Ovid provides two etymologies लिये जून 's नाम in his poem concerning the months entitled the Fasti.
The पहला is कि the माह is named बाद the Roman देवी juno, wife of बृहस्पति and समतुल्य to the Greek goddess hera ; the दूसरी is कि the नाम आता इससे the Latin शब्द iuniores, meaning `` younger ones, '' as opposed to maiores ( `` बड़ो '' ) for जिससे the preceding माह May may be नामित ( Fasti vi.1–88 ).
देखिए : Months in विभिन्न पंचांग also called the ऋतु of the जून is the month with the longest daylight घंटों of the year in the उत्तरी गोलार्ध और the shortest daylight घंटों of the साल in the दक्षिणी गोलार्ध.
जून in the Northern गोलार्ध is the seasonal समतुल्य to December in the Southern गोलार्ध और vice versa.
In the उत्तरी hemisphere, the beginning of the meteorological गर्मियाँ is 1 June.
In the Southern hemisphere, the शुरूआत of the meteorological शीत is 1 जून.
at the start of जून, the सूर्य उदय in the constellation of वृष ; at the end of जून, the sun rises in the constellation of मिथुन.
however, due to the precession of the equinoxes, जून begins साथ the सूर्य in the astrological sign of मिथुन, और ends with the sun in the astrological चिह्न of कर्कट.
जून is known for the विशाल क्रमांक of विवाह that occur over the कोर्स of the माह.
According to एक etymology, जून is named बाद juno ( Hera ).
juno थी the देवी of विवाह और a शादीशुदा युगल 's household, so some consider it शुभ luck to be शादीशुदा in इस माह.
according to another etymology provided by the Roman poet ओविड, June is named लिये the iuniores, latin लिये `` young people '' ( fasti vi.88 ) and that the माह of may is named for the maiores, Latin लिये `` बड़ो ''.
In आइसलैंड, folklore says that if तुम bathe नग्न in the morning ओस on the morning of June 24, तुम हैं supposed to रखना aging at खाड़ी लिये longer.
a constitution is a set of fundamental सिद्धान्त or स्थापित precedents according to जिससे a state or other organization is governed.
ये rules साथ मेक up, i.e. constitute, what the entity is.
जब ये सिद्धान्त are लिखा down into a सिंगल दस्तावेज़ or नियत of legal documents, those documents may be said to embody a written संविधान ; if वे हैं लिखा down in a single comprehensive दस्तावेज़, it is said to embody a संहिताबद्ध constitution.
constitutions concern different स्तर of organizations, इससे sovereign states to कंपनियाँ and unincorporated एसोसिएशन.
a सन्धि जिससे establishes an अंतरराष्ट्रीय संगठन is also its constitution, in कि it होता define कैसा that संगठन is constituted.
भीतर states, whether sovereign or federated, a constitution defines the principles upon जिससे the राज्य is आधारित, the कार्यविधि in which कानून हैं made और by जिसको.
कुछ constitutions, especially संहिताबद्ध constitutions, also अधिनियम as limiters of state शक्ति, by establishing लाइनों जिससे a राज्य 's शासकों can not cross, ऐसे as आधारभूत rights.
जार्ज वॉशिंगटन at संवैधानिक सम्मेलन of 1787, हस्ताक्षर of U.S. Constitution.
the संविधान of इण्डिया is the longest लिखा संविधान of कोई sovereign देश in the world, containing 448 articles, 12 schedules and 100 amendments, साथ 117,369 words in its English भाषा version, जबकि the संयुक्त States संविधान is the shortest लिखा constitution, at 7 आलेख और 27 amendments.

Engineering management is a specialized form of प्रबन्धन that is चिंतित साथ the अनुप्रयोग of अभियान्त्रिकी principles to business अभ्यास.
अभियान्त्रिकी management is a करियर कि brings together the technological problem-solving savvy of engineering और the organizational, प्रशासनिक, और नियोजन abilities of प्रबन्धन in अनुक्रम to oversee complex enterprises इससे धारणा to पूर्णता.
Example क्षेत्रों of engineering are उत्पाद विकास, manufacturing, construction, design अभियान्त्रिकी, industrial अभियान्त्रिकी, प्रौद्योगिकी, production, or any अन्य field कि employs कर्मियों who perform an engineering फलन.
कामयाब अभियान्त्रिकी managers typically आवश्यकता प्रशिक्षण और अनुभव in कारोबार और engineering.
Technically inept managers tend to be deprived of support by उनके technical टोली, और non-commercial प्रबंधक tend to कमी commercial acumen to उद्धार in a मार्केट अर्थव्यवस्था.
Largely, engineering प्रबंधक manage engineers who हैं driven by non-entrepreneurial सोच, यूँ आवश्यकता the जरुरी लोगों skills to coach, mentor and motivate technical professionals.
अभियान्त्रिकी पेशेवर joining निर्माण companies sometimes become अभियान्त्रिकी प्रबंधक by डिफॉल्ट after a काल of time.
वे हैं required to सीख कैसा to मैनेज once वे are on the job, हालांकि इस is प्रायः an अप्रभावी way to develop managerial abilities.
in an insurance policy, the deductible is the राशि of खर्च that जरूर be paid out of pocket before an insurer होगा अदा कोई खर्च.
in सामान्य उपयोग, the पद deductible may be प्रयुक्त to describe एक of several प्रकार of clauses ( देखिए नीचे ) कि are प्रयुक्त by insurance कंपनियाँ as a दहलीज लिये नीति भुगतान.
deductibles हैं typically प्रयुक्त to deter the large क्रमांक of trivial दावा कि a उपभोक्ता can be reasonably expected to bear the लागत of.
By restricting इसके कवरेज to कार्यक्रम कि हैं significant enough to incur large लागत, the बीमे कड़ expects to अदा आउट slightly छोटी amounts much कम अक्सर, रूष्ट much higher savings.
as a result, बीमे premiums हैं typically सस्ता when वे involve उच्चतर deductibles.
deductibles are normally provided as clauses in an बीमे नीति कि dictate how much of an insurance-covered व्यय is borne by the policyholder.
वे are सामान्यतः कोटेड as a फिक्स्ड मात्रा और is a part of सबसे policies covering losses to the नीति holder.
The insurer तब becomes liable लिये claimable expenses कि exceed इस राशि ( विषय to the maximum योग claimable indicated in the अनुबंध ).
Depending on the policy, the deductible may apply per covered incident, or प्रति year.
लिये नीतियों जहाँ incidences हैं not आसान to delimit ( for example health insurance ), the deductible is typically applied per साल.
अनेक deductibles can be नियत by the insurer based on the cause of the अर्जी.
लिये उदाहरण, a सिंगल housing insurance policy may contain multiple deductible amounts for घाटा or क्षति arising इससे चोरी, आग, प्राकृतिक calamities, evacuation etc.
वहीँ हैं also deductible reimbursement कार्यक्रम कि reimburse a deductible in the event of an स्वचालित, घर, boat/yacht or health बीमे अर्जी.
An invoice or विधेयक is a वाणिज्यिक दस्तावेज़ issued by a विक्रेता to a buyer, indicating the उत्पाद, quantities, and agreed कीमतें for products or सेवाएं the विक्रेता has provided the buyer.
an चालान indicates the बिक्री transaction तभी.
Payment शर्तें are स्वतंत्र of the चालान और हैं negotiated by the buyer and the विक्रेता.
भुगतान शर्तें हैं प्रायः included on the चालान.
the खरीदार could have already सशुल्क लिये the उत्पाद or services listed on the चालान.
खरीदार can भी have a maximum क्रमांक of दिनों in which to pay लिये these goods और is sometimes offered a छूट if paid before the due तिथि.
in the rental industry, an invoice जरूर शामिल a विशिष्ट सन्दर्भ to the अवधि of the समय being billed, so in जोड to मात्रा, दाम and discount the invoicing amount is भी आधारित on अवधि.
Generally प्रत्येक लकीर of a rental चालान will refer to the वास्तविक घंटों, दिनों, सप्ताह, महीने, etc., होने billed.
From the पाइंट of दृश्य of a विक्रेता, an चालान is a sales invoice.
From the point of view of a buyer, an invoice is a खरीदें चालान.
the दस्तावेज़ indicates the खरीदार और विक्रेता, लकिन the पद चालान indicates money is owed or owing.
In अंग्रेज़ी, the context of the पद चालान is प्रायः प्रयुक्त to clarify its meaning, ऐसे as `` We sent them an चालान '' ( वे owe us money ) or `` we प्राप्त an invoice from उन्हें '' ( we owe उन्हें धन ).
The right प्रमुख bronchus ( or सही primary bronchus, or सही principal bronchus ) is a bronchus of the respiratory system.
it is wider, shorter, और अधिक vertical in दिशा than the बाएँ.
It is परिचय 2.5 cm long, and enters the सही lung nearly opposite the पांचवां thoracic vertebra.
The azygos vein arches over it इससे behind ; और the सही pulmonary धमनी झूठ at first below और then in front of it.
About 2 cm from इसके शुरुआत it देता off a branch to the अपर पालि of the right फेफड़ों.
इस is termed the eparterial शाखा of the bronchus, क्युकी it arises above the सही pulmonary artery.
the bronchus now passes नीचे the artery, और is ज्ञात as the hyparterial शाखा ; it divides into दो branches लिये the मध्य और निम्नतर lobes.
if a foreign body in the airway गुजरता through the श्वासनली, it होगा most संभावित enter the right main bronchus बजाय of the बाएँ, due to the straighter संरेखण of the right bronchus to the trachea.
Squash is a racquet खेल played by two ( singles ) or चार players ( युगल ) in a four-walled अदालत with a small, खोखला रबर बॉल.
the खिलाड़ी जरूर वैकल्पिक in striking the ball with उनके racquet and hit the बॉल onto the playable सतहों of the चार दीवारें of the अदालत.
the game was formerly पुकारा स्क्वैश racquets, a सन्दर्भ to the `` squashable '' नरम बॉल प्रयुक्त in the game ( compared साथ the fatter बॉल प्रयुक्त in its जनक खेल racquets or rackets ).
Squash is recognized by the ioc and supporters are lobbying लिये इसके incorporation in a भविष्य Olympic कार्यक्रम.
in 2003, फोर्ब्स rated स्क्वैश as the क्रमांक एक healthiest खेल to खेल.
अवशेष oil is oil found in low एकाग्रता naturally or in बेहाल आयल फ़ील्ड.
Often मिश्रित साथ जल, it can not be recovered by conventional तकनीकों.
however, it can be recovered using carbon dioxide-enhanced oil रिकवरी ( co2 EOR ) जिससे involves injecting carbon dioxide into the well reducing viscosity और बढ़ाना प्रवाह of the आयल.
the technique is नहीं new लकिन रै नहीं महरूम प्रयुक्त extensively on residual oil zones, low-grade जमा of petroleum ऐसे as the 38 वर्गाकार मील in the permian Basin of टेक्सास leased by elliott रूज़वेल्ट jr.
The technique is limited by उपलब्धता of carbon डाइऑक्साइड.
It does नहीं result in sequestration of the कार्बन dioxide but the gas is recycled as much as संभावित.
संयुक्त States reserves of residual आयल हैं अनुमानित to be 100 अरब barrels.

the ग्रेट शिकागो आग थी a conflagration that burned इससे संडे, अक्तूबर 8, to जल्दी मंगलवार, October 10, 1871, हत्या hundreds and destroying परिचय in शिकागो, इलिनोइस.
हालांकि the fire थी एक of the largest u.S. आपदाओं of the 19th century, the rebuilding that began helped develop शिकागो as एक of the सबसे populous and economically important American शहरों.
Henry VIII ( 28 जून 1491 – 28 जनवरी 1547 ) was king of इंग्लैण्ड इससे 21 April 1509 जबतक उसके death.
he थी lord, and बाद king, of आयरलैंड, as well as continuing the nominal अर्जी by the English monarchs to the किंगडम of France.
Henry was the दूसरी monarch of the ट्यूडर राजवंश, succeeding his पिता, Henry सात.
Besides उसके छह marriages, हेनरी VIII is ज्ञात for उसके भूमिका in the विरह of the Church of इंग्लैण्ड इससे the Roman कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर.
हेनरी 's struggles साथ रोम led to the separation of the गिरिजाघर of इंग्लैण्ड from papal प्राधिकार, the विच्छेद of the monasteries, और उसके अपना establishment as the परम् Head of the गिरिजाघर of इंग्लैण्ड.
yet he remained a आस्तिक in कोर Catholic theological शिक्षाओं, even बाद his excommunication इससे the Roman कैथोलिक गिरिजाघर.
Henry oversaw the विधिक union of इंग्लैण्ड और वेल्स साथ the Laws in Wales Acts 1535 और 1542.
in 1513, the नई king अलाइड साथ the पावन Roman सम्राट, Maximillian I, और invaded France in 1513 with a large, well-equipped फौज, लकिन हासिल little at a considerable financial लागत.
maximillian, लिये his भाग, used the अंग्रेज़ी आक्रमण to उसके own ends, and इस prejudiced England 's ability to defeat the फ्रेंच.
इस foray would prove the प्रारंभ of an obsession for हेनरी, who invaded again in 1544.
इस time, Henry 's forces captured the important city of Boulogne, but again the Holy रोमन सम्राट, चार्ल्स v, समर्थित Henry तभी as long as he needed to and England, strained by the enormous cost of the युद्ध, ransomed the नगर back for सलाम.
उसके contemporaries माना हेनरी in his प्रधान to be an आकर्षक, educated and संपन्नता king, और he has been वर्णित as `` एक of the सबसे charismatic शासकों to बैठना on the अंग्रेज़ी throne ''.
besides ruling साथ absolute power, he also सगाई खुद as an author और composer.
His ख्वाहिश to provide इंग्लैण्ड साथ a पुरूष heir – which stemmed partly इससे personal vanity and partly क्युकी he believed a daughter होता be unable to consolidate the ट्यूडर राजवंश and the fragile peace that existed following the Wars of the Roses – led to the दो बाते लिये which हेनरी is most remembered : उसके छह marriages और the अंग्रेज़ी reformation.
हेनरी became morbidly obese और उसके स्वास्थ्य suffered, contributing to his death in 1547.
he is अक्सर characterised in his later जीवन as a lustful, egotistical, harsh, and असुरक्षित किंग.
la Reina डेल सूर ( the महारानी of the दक्षिण ) is a spanish-language telenovela produced by the संयुक्त राज्य टेलीविज़न संजाल telemundo, in संयोजन with the Antena 3 संजाल और rti producciones.
Based on a अनोखा of the same name by स्पेनी author arturo pérez-reverte, the drama depicts the वृद्धि of Teresa मेंडोज़ा ( केट del Castillo ), a यंग woman from Mexico जो becomes the most शक्तिशाली ड्रग trafficker in दक्षिणी स्पेन.
Patricio Wills, the अध्यक्ष of telemundo टेलीविज़न Studios, थी the कार्यपालिका producer.
हालांकि la Reina डेल सूर was मनोनीत for novela of the साल, पसंदीदा सीसे अभिनेत्री, and बेहतरीन Bad Luck वीडियो, it won no पुरस्कार.
साथ a $ 10 लाख budget, La reina del सूर थी the most expensive telenovela ever produced by Telemundo.
The program 's premiere on February 28, 2011, थी the संजाल 's उच्चतम रेटेड premiere for a telenovela to तिथि.
the कार्यक्रम अक्सर वर्चस्व इसके समय स्लॉट, भी over English language प्रोग्रामिंग on other प्रमुख u.S. संजाल.
la reina डेल Sur समाप्त its 63 episode run on telemundo और इसके 13 एपीसोड चलाएं on एंटेना 3 simultaneously on may 30, 2011.
The फाइनल episode was the उच्चतम rated broadcast in telemundo 's 19-year history ( 4.2 million दर्शक ), और ताल सब of the English भाषा u.S. television संजाल to earn the क्रमांक एक स्लॉट in the 18-49 adult जनसांख्यिकी.
The कार्यक्रम 's success spurred Telemundo to लॉन्च its पहला campaign to gain the series an एमी पुरस्कार नामांकन.
A one-night खास featuring अनेक cast सदस्यों aired on May 31, 2011, and marked the telemundo डेब्यू of विख्यात Latina टेलीविज़न व्यक्तित्व Cristina Saralegui.
la Reina डेल Sur is broadcast in several other बाज़ार, सहित सर्बिया, Colombia, Chile, साइप्रस, निकारागुआ, कोस्टा रिका, Mexico, अल्बानियाई, हंगेरियाई, Slovenia, क्रोएशिया, Romania, ( among others ).

a वेब होस्टिंग सेवा is a प्रकार of अंतरजाल hosting service कि allows individuals and संगठन to मेक their website accessible via the संसार चौड़ी Web.
Web होस्ट हैं कंपनियाँ कि provide स्पेस on a सर्वर owned or leased लिये use by क्लाइंट, as खूब as providing Internet कनेक्टिविटी, typically in a आंकड़ा बीच.
Web hosts can also provide आंकड़ा बीच space और कनेक्टिविटी to the अंतरजाल for other servers स्तिथ in उनके आंकड़ा center, पुकारा colocation, भी known as आवास in Latin अमेरिका or फ़्रांस.
the पैमाना of web होस्टिंग services varies greatly.
the most basic is वेब पेज और small-scale file hosting, जहाँ फाइलें can be अपलोड via File ट्रांसफ़र Protocol ( एफटीपी ) or a वेब इंटरफ़ेस.
The फाइलें हैं usually वितरित to the वेब `` as is '' or with minimal processing.
अनेक अंतरजाल सेवा providers ( isps ) offer इस service फ़्री to subscribers.
Individuals और organizations may also obtain वेब पेज hosting इससे alternative सेवा providers.
निजी web साईट होस्टिंग is typically free, advertisement-sponsored, or inexpensive.
कारोबार वेब site होस्टिंग often रै a उच्चतर expense depending upon the आकार और प्रकार of the जालस्थल.
Single page होस्टिंग is generally sufficient लिये personal वेब pages.
a जटिल साईट काल्स for a अधिक व्यापक पैकेज कि provides डेटाबेस support और application development platforms ( e.g. पीएचपी, जावा, माणिक्य on rails, coldfusion, or ASP.NET ).
ये सुविधाएं allow customers to लिखें or install scripts लिये अनुप्रयोग जैसे forums and सामग्री प्रबन्धन.
भी, Secure sockets Layer ( एसएसएल ) is typically प्रयुक्त लिये e-commerce.
The host may भी provide an interface or कंट्रोल फलक for मैनेजिंग the Web server and installing scripts, as well as other modules and service अनुप्रयोग like e-mail.
कुछ hosts specialize in निश्चित तन्त्र or सेवाएं ( e.g. e-commerce ), जिससे are commonly प्रयुक्त by larger companies कि outsource संजाल अवसंरचना.
मैडेन NFL ( ज्ञात as जॉन Madden Football पहले 1993 ) is an American फ़ुटबॉल वीडियो खेल series विकसित by Electronic कला tiburon for ea Sports.
The खेल श्रेणी is named बाद प्रो फ़ुटबॉल हॉल of famer जॉन Madden, a well-known पूर्व सुपर कटोरी –winning coach of the Oakland हमलावरों और color commentator.
the श्रेणी is the best selling EA Sports series.
the games have consistently been a बेहतरीन seller, और has even शाखित TV shows जहाँ players compete.
among the game 's यथार्थवादी सुविधाएँ include sophisticated playbooks and खिलाड़ी आंकडे, और voice commentary कि allows खिलाड़ी to सुन the game as if it यहूद a रियल tv broadcast.
The Madden एनएफएल series रै महरूम nicknamed the NFL 's 33rd मताधिकार.
the श्रेणी थी originally conceived by इलेक्ट्रॉनिक कला संस्थापक ट्रिप हॉकिन्स, जो then approached मैडेन in 1984 लिये उसके समर्थन और विशेषज्ञता.
Due to मैडेन 's insistence कि the खेल be as यथार्थवादी as संभावित, the पहला संस्करण of जॉन Madden Football was not released जबतक 1988.
The second संस्करण of the खेल was released in 1990, with सालाना versions चूंकि तब.
the series ' नाम थी changed to Madden NFL in 1993 बाद ea acquired the rights to use NFL teams और players.
despite मैडेन 's रिटायरमेंट as a प्रसारणकर्ता in 2009, he continues to lend उसके नाम और provide expertise लिये the खेल.
Cindy Lee Miller Sheehan ( born जुलाई 10, 1957 ) is an American antiwar activist whose बेटे, u.S. फौज Specialist केसी Sheehan, was मारे by enemy कार्रवाई during the इराकी युद्ध.

in law, a set-off is a statutory रक्षा to the पूरे or to a portion of a अभियोक्ता 's claim.
It had no existence अंतर्गत the अंग्रेज़ी common विधि, होने created by 2 जियो. ii c. 22 लिये the राहत of insolvent कर्जदार, although set-off थी पहचाना in equity.
Such a defense could be pleaded only in respect of परस्पर debts of a definite अक्षर, और did नहीं apply to मामले in जिससे damages यहूद claimed, nor to निष्पक्ष दावा or मांगे.
by the rules of the Supreme Court ( O. xix. r. 3 ) a defendant in an कार्रवाई may set off or set up कोई right or claim by way of counterclaim विरूद्ध the दावा of a अभियोक्ता, and ऐसे set-off or counterclaim रै the वही effect as a बयान of claim in a cross-action.
the legal defense of set-off ( ऊपर ) थी originally introduced to prevent the unfair situation whereby a person ( `` पार्टी a '' ) जो owed धन to another ( `` पार्टी b '' ) could be भेजा to कर्जदार थाना, despite the fact कि Party B also owed धन to Party A.
The विधि thus allows दोनो पार्टियों to टालना भुगतान जबतक उनके संबंधित claims have been सुना in अदालत.
Upon निर्णय, both दावा हैं बुझे and replaced by a सिंगल net योग owing ( e.g. if Party A owes पार्टी b 100 and Party b owes Party a 105, the दो रकम हैं set off and replaced साथ a सिंगल दायित्व of 5 from पार्टी b to पार्टी a ).
set-off can also be incorporated by contractual अनुबंध so that, where a पार्टी मूलभूत, the परस्पर amounts owing हैं automatically set off और बुझे.
In certain jurisdictions ( सहित the UK ), set-off takes प्लेस automatically upon the insolvency of a कम्पनी.
This means that, लिये each पार्टी जिससे is both a creditor and debtor of the insolvent company, परस्पर debts हैं set-off विरूद्ध each अन्य, और तब either the bankrupt 's creditor can claim the balance in the दिवालियापन or the ट्रस्टी in bankruptcy can ask लिये the संतुलन remaining to be सशुल्क, depending on which पक्ष owed the most.
This has महरूम criticized as an undeclared सुरक्षा ब्याज कि violates the principle of परी passu.
the वैकल्पिक, where a creditor has to अदा सब इसके debts, but receive only a limited portion of the leftover moneys कि other unsecured creditors मिलेंगी, मुद्राएँ the खतरे of 'knock-on ' insolvencies.
The right to नियत off is particularly important when रिपोर्टिंग a bank 's विकिरणों to regulatory अधिकारियों.
The हालात where a bank has to रपट that it has lent a large योग to a borrower ( and is इसलिए exposed, because वहीँ is a रिस्क that the borrower might default thereby अग्रणी to the घाटा of the बैंको 's or its जमाकर्ताओं ' money ) is thus replaced ( where the bank रै लिया सुरक्षा over साझा or प्रतिभूति of the borrower ) साथ an एक्सपोज़र of the धन lent ऋण the मान of the सुरक्षा लिया.
जेनिफर joanna एनिस्टन ( born February 11, 1969 ) is an अमरीकी अभिनेत्री, film director, and producer.
एनिस्टन gained worldwide मान्यता in the 1990s for portraying रेचल ग्रीन on the टेलीविज़न sitcom मित्रों, a भूमिका which earned उसके an एमी Award, a Golden ग्लोब Award, और a स्क्रीन अभिनेताओं गिल्ड पुरस्कार.
एनिस्टन रै also enjoyed a कामयाब हॉलीवुड फिल्मी करियर.
She gained नाजुक acclaim for her performances in the independent films वो 's the One ( 1996 ), दफ्तर स्पेस ( 1999 ), the शुभ लड़की ( 2002 ) और मित्रों with धन ( 2006 ).
She रै था उसके greatest वाणिज्यिक successes साथ the films Bruce सर्वशक्तिमान ( 2003 ), The Break-Up ( 2006 ), Marley & me ( 2008 ), Just go with It ( 2011 ) and भयानक Bosses ( 2011 ).
एनिस्टन प्राप्त a स्टार on the Hollywood Walk of Fame on फ़रवरी 22, 2012.
a श्वेत Bengal बाघ at the ह्यूस्टन एक्वेरियम
( वीडियो )
A श्वेत tiger at Tobu Zoo, in saitama, जापानी.
the श्वेत tiger is a recessive mutant of the बंगाल बाघ, जिससे was reported in the wild इससे समय to time in असम, बंगाल, Bihar और विशेषकर from the पूर्व State of रीवा.
Conventional पीसीआई ( पीसीआई is an initialism formed from परिधीय घटक Interconnect, भाग of the PCI Local बस मानक और often shortened to बस PCI ) is a लोकल कंप्यूटर बस लिये attaching हार्डवेयर डिवाइस in a computer.
The PCI बस supports the functions मिला on a processor बस, लकिन in a मानकीकृत स्वरूप कि is स्वतंत्र of any particular प्रोसेसर.
Devices कनेक्ट to the bus appear to the processor to be कनेक्ट सीधे to the processor बस, और हैं आबंटित addresses in the processor 's पता स्पेस.
संलग्न devices can लो either the रूप of an integrated सर्किट fitted onto the मदरबोर्ड itself, पुकारा a planar यंत्र in the पीसीआई specification, or an expansion कार्ड कि fits into a स्लॉट.
the PCI Local Bus was पहला implemented in IBM PC compatibles, जहाँ it विस्थापित the संयोजन of ISA प्लस one vesa लोकल बस as the बस विन्यास.
It रै subsequently महरूम adopted for other कंप्यूटर types.
PCI and PCI-X are होने replaced by पीसीआई एक्स्प्रेस, लकिन, most motherboards are स्टिल बना साथ एक or अधिक PCI slots, which हैं sufficient लिये many उपयोग.
The पीसीआई specification कवर the शारीरिक size of the बस ( including the size and अंतरण of the सर्किट फलक edge विद्युत सम्पर्क ), electrical विशेषताएँ, बस समय, और protocols.
the specification can be purchased इससे the PCI खास Interest समूह ( PCI-SIG ).
ठेठ PCI cards प्रयुक्त in PCs include : network ताश, sound cards, modems, अतिरिक्त पोर्ट such as USB or serial, tv ट्यूनर ताश and डिस्क परिरक्षक.
PCI वीडियो ताश replaced ISA and vesa cards, जबतक growing बैंडविड्थ आवश्यकताएँ outgrew the सामर्थ्य of पीसीआई ; the पसन्दीदा इंटरफ़ेस लिये वीडियो cards became अगप, और तब पीसीआई एक्स्प्रेस.
PCI video ताश remain available लिये उपयोग with old pcs without अगप or पीसीआई एक्स्प्रेस स्लॉट.
Many डिवाइस previously provided on PCI विस्तार cards हैं now commonly एकीकृत onto motherboards or available in universal serial बस और PCI Express versions.
Caffeine is a bitter, श्वेत crystalline xanthine एल्कलॉएड कि अधिनियमों as a stimulant ड्रग.
कैफीन is found in varying quantities in the seeds, leaves, और फल of कुछ पौधे, where it अधिनियमों as a प्राकृतिक pesticide कि paralyzes और मारता निश्चित insects feeding on the पौधे, as खूब as बढ़ाना the बदला मेमोरी of pollinators.
It is most commonly consumed by इंसानो in infusions निकाली from the बीज of the coffee संयंत्र और the leaves of the tea बुश, as खूब as इससे विभिन्न भोजन and drinks containing उत्पाद derived इससे the कोला नट.
अन्य स्त्रोत शामिल yerba maté, guarana berries, guayusa, और the yaupon होली.
in इंसानो, कैफीन acts as a central बेचैन प्रणाली उत्तेजक, temporarily warding बंद drowsiness and restoring alertness.
it is the संसार 's सबसे widely consumed psychoactive drug, लकिन unlike अनेक other psychoactive substances, it is विधिक and unregulated in nearly all भाग of the संसार.
पेय containing कैफीन, such as coffee, tea, soft पेय, और energy drinks, enjoy great लोकप्रियता.
in उत्तर अमेरिका, 90 % of वयस्कों consume caffeine रोज़.
भाग of the reason कैफीन is वर्गीकृत by the Food and ड्रग Administration as ग्रा ( generally पहचाना as सुरक्षित ) is that toxic doses ( over 10 grams ) are much उच्चतर than typically used doses ( less than 500 milligrams ).
Ordinary consumption can have low health risks, भी जब carried on लिये years – there may be a modest protective प्रभाव against कुछ रोगों, सहित parkinsons Disease, और certain प्रकार of कर्कट.
कैफीन can have दोनो positive and ऋणात्मक प्रभाव on चिंता विकार.
Some लोगों अनुभव नींद disruption if वे consume कैफीन, especially during the evening hours, लकिन others show छोटी disturbance and the प्रभाव of caffeine on sleep is highly परिवर्तनीय.

With भारी उपयोग, सहिष्णुता develops rapidly to autonomic प्रभाव ऐसे as elevated heart रेट और मांसपेशी twitching, लकिन नहीं to the संज्ञानात्मक or arousal effects of caffeine.

A आग सचेतक Control फलक ( FACP ), or आग सचेतक Control ईकाई ( FACU ), is the controlling घटक of a आग सचेतक प्रणाली.
The फलक receives सूचना इससे पर्यावरणीय sensors designed to detect परिवर्तन संबद्ध with आग, मॉनीटर उनके operational अखंडता और provides लिये स्वचालित control of equipment, और हस्तांतरण of सूचना जरुरी to prepare the facility for आग आधारित on a predetermined sequence.
the फलक may भी सप्लाई विद्युत energy to operate any संबद्ध sensor, कंट्रोल, transmitter, or रिले.

Black swan is a 2010 अमरीकी मनोवैज्ञानिक थ्रिलर and horror फिल्मी निर्देशित by डैरेन aronofsky and अभिनीत नताली पोर्टमैन, विंसेंट cassel, and mila kunis.
the प्लाट revolves around a production of tchaikovsky 's swan Lake बैले by a prestigious नई यॉर्क नगर company.
the production requires a नर्तकी to खेल the निर्दोष और नाजुक श्वेत swan, लिये which the वचनबद्ध नर्तकी Nina ( Portman ) is a पूर्ण अनुरूप, as well as the dark and कामुक ब्लैक swan, which हैं qualities embodied by the नई arrival Lily ( Kunis ).
Nina is overwhelmed by a feeling of immense दबाव when she पाता herself स्पर्धा for the भाग, causing her to lose उसके tenuous grip on reality और descend into a living nightmare.
Aronofsky conceived the premise by connecting उसके viewings of a उत्पादन of swan झील with an unrealized screenplay about understudies और the notion of being haunted by a दोगुना, similar to the folklore surrounding doppelgängers.
aronofsky cites fyodor Dostoyevsky 's `` The दोगुना `` as another प्रेरणा लिये the फिल्मी.
The निदेशक भी considered Black Swan a companion टुकड़ा to उसके 2008 film the पहलवान, साथ दोनो films involving demanding प्रदर्शन लिये different kinds of art.
he और Portman first discussed the प्रोजेक्ट in 2000, और बाद a brief अनुलग्नक to सार्वभौमिक Studios, Black swan थी produced in New यॉर्क नगर in 2009 by फॉक्स searchlight तस्वीरें.
Portman और kunis प्रशिक्षित in ballet लिये अनेक months prior to फिल्मांकन, और notable आंकड़े इससे the ballet world helped साथ film उत्पादन to shape the ballet presentation.
The फिल्मी premiered as the खोलने film for the 67th वेनिस International फिल्मी Festival on September 1, 2010.

in जोड, the film itself प्राप्त a नामांकन लिये बेहतरीन Picture.
The world’s पहला ice-calorimeter, प्रयुक्त in the winter of 1782-83, by एंटोनी Lavoisier और Pierre-Simon लाप्लास, to determine the heat शामिल in various रासायनिक परिवर्तन ; calculations जिससे यहूद आधारित on Joseph Black ’s prior डिस्कवरी of अदृश्य ऊष्मा.
ये experiments चिह्नित the न्यास of thermochemistry.
A calorimeter ( इससे Latin calor, अर्थ ऊष्मा ) is an ऑब्जेक्ट प्रयुक्त लिये calorimetry, or the process of measuring the heat of रासायनिक प्रतिक्रियाएँ or physical changes as खूब as ऊष्मा capacity.
अवकल स्कैनिंग calorimeters, समतापी microcalorimeters, titration calorimeters और accelerated रेट calorimeters हैं among the most आम types.
a सरल ऊष्मामापी बस consists of a थर्मामीटर attached to a मेटल container पूरा of जल निलंबित above a combustion chamber.
to find the enthalpy बदलें प्रति mole of a पदार्थ A in a reaction between two substances a and b, the substances are added to a ऊष्मामापी और the initial and फाइनल temperatures ( before the प्रतिक्रिया प्रारंभ और बाद it रै finished ) are विख्यात.
multiplying the तापमान बदलें by the द्रव्यमान and विशिष्ट heat capacities of the substances देता a मान लिये the उर्जा given off or अवशोषित during the प्रतिक्रिया.
dividing the energy बदलें by कैसा अनेक औज़ार of A were present देता its enthalpy change of प्रतिक्रिया.
This method is प्रयुक्त primarily in अकादमिक शिक्षण as it describes the सिद्धान्त of कैलोरीमिति.
it करता नहीं खाता लिये the ऊष्मा घाटा through the container or the heat क्षमता of the thermometer और संग्राहक itself.
In addition, the ऑब्जेक्ट placed inside the calorimeter shows that the वस्तुएँ transferred उनके ऊष्मा to the ऊष्मामापी and into the द्रव, और the ऊष्मा absorbed by the calorimeter and the द्रव is equal to the ऊष्मा given बंद by the metals.
a pair of ग्रीन flip-flops
Flip-flops ( भी पुकारा zōri, thongs, jandals, or a किस्में of अन्य names throughout the world ) हैं a type of open-toed चन्दन typically worn in कैज़ुअल situations, such as outside or at the बीच.
वे consist of a flat एकमात्र आयोजित loosely on the foot by a Y-shaped strap कि गुजरता between the पहला और second toes और around either side of the foot.
वे may also be held to the पैर साथ a सिंगल डोरी over the front of the पैर rather than a thong.
the name `` flip-flop '' originated because of the ध्वनि कि is made by slapping between the sole of the foot and the मंजिल जब walking.
This स्टाइल of जूते has been worn by the लोगों of अनेक cultures throughout the संसार, originating as early as the प्राचीन उन्होंने in 4,000 b.c.
the modern flip-flop उतरता from the Japanese zōri, which became popular बाद संसार War II when सैनिको returning to the संयुक्त राज्य brought उन्हें back.
वे became लोकप्रिय in कैज़ुअल settings during the 1960s, 1990s, और 2000s, और कुछ varieties have भी मिला उनके रास्ता into more औपचारिक पहनावा, despite आलोचना.
the उपयोग of flip-flops can परिणाम in अनेक pains और चोटों, including ankle sprains और broken bones.
Some individuals who चलना for long अवधि report pain in the फीट, ankles, और lower legs.
The कमी of support provided by flip-flops प्रायः results in over-pronation चोटों, caused by the पैर slipping inwards further than normal.
इस can सीसे to flat फीट और tendonitis.
अन्य injuries कि may परिणाम are due to the जूते 's open-toed nature, such as stubbed toes, कटौती, and bruises.

The law of सामान्य औसत is a legal principle of मेरीटाइम law according to जिससे all parties in a sea venture proportionally share कोई losses resulting इससे a voluntary बलिदान of भाग of the ship or कार्गो to सहेजें the whole in an आपात.
in the exigencies of hazards faced at समुद्र, crew members प्रायः have अनमोल छोटी समय in जिससे to determine precisely whose कार्गो वे हैं jettisoning.
यूँ, to avoid quarrelling कि could बर्बाद valuable time, वहीँ arose the निष्पक्ष अभ्यास whereby all the merchants जिनकी cargo उतरा सकुशल would be पुकारा on to contribute a portion, based upon a share or प्रतिशत, to the व्यापारी or merchants जिनकी goods था been tossed overboard to avert निकट peril.
जबकि सामान्य औसत traces इसके origins in प्राचीन maritime विधि, स्टिल it remains भाग of the admiralty विधि of most देशों.
The पहला codification of सामान्य average थी the यॉर्क Antwerp नियम of 1890.
American कंपनियाँ स्वीकृत it in 1949.
सामान्य औसत requires तीन elements जिससे are clearly stated by mr. इंसाफ grier in बर्नार्ड v. आदमs:
`` 1st.
A आम खतरे : a danger in जिससे vessel, कार्गो और crew सब participate ; a danger निकट and जाहिर 'inevitable, ' मगर by voluntarily रूष्ट the घाटा of a portion of the whole to सहेजें the शेष. ''
`` 2nd. There must be a voluntary jettison, jactus, or casting away, of कुछ portion of the joint concern for the purpose of avoiding this imminent peril, periculi imminentis evitandi causa, or, in other शब्द, a transfer of the peril इससे the पूरे to a particular portion of the पूरे. ''
`` 3rd.
इस attempt to avoid the निकट आम peril जरूर be कामयाब ''.
उदाहरण Polish कॉल for टीकाकरण विरूद्ध डिप्थीरिया और Tetanus.
A vaccination अनुसूची is a श्रेणी of vaccinations, including the समय of सब doses, जिससे may be either अनुशंसित or compulsory, depending on the देश of residence.
a टीका is an antigenic preparation प्रयुक्त to उपज active immunity to a बीमारी, in अनुक्रम to prevent or reduce the प्रभाव of संक्रमण by any प्राकृतिक or `` wild '' pathogen.
Many टीके require multiple doses लिये अधिकतम effectiveness, either to उपज sufficient आरंभिक प्रतिरक्षा जवाब or to बूस्ट जवाब कि fades over time.
लिये example, tetanus टीका boosters are often recommended प्रत्येक 10 years.
Vaccine schedules हैं विकसित by governmental agencies or physicians समूह to achieve अधिकतम effectiveness using required और अनुशंसित टीके for a locality जबकि महती the क्रमांक of health परवाह प्रणाली interactions.
Over the पास्ट two दशकों, the recommended टीकाकरण अनुसूची रै grown rapidly और become अधिक जटिल as many नई vaccines have been विकसित.
कुछ vaccines हैं recommended only in निश्चित क्षेत्रों ( countries, subnational क्षेत्रों, or at-risk populations ) जहाँ a बीमारी is आम.
लिये उदाहरण, yellow fever टीकाकरण is on the दिनचर्या टीका अनुसूची of French guiana, is अनुशंसित in certain regions of Brazil but in the United राज्य is only दिए to travelers heading to देशों साथ a इतिहास of the बीमारी.
in विकासशील countries, टीका सुझाव also लो into खाता the स्तर of health परवाह अभिगम, the cost of टीके and issues साथ टीका उपलब्धता और भंडार.
Sample vaccinations schedules discussed by the संसार स्वास्थ्य संगठन show a विकसित देश using a अनुसूची जिससे extends over the पहला पाँच years of a child 's जीवन और उपयोग टीके जिससे लागत over $ 700 including प्रशासन costs while a विकासशील देश उपयोग a अनुसूची providing vaccines in the पहला 9 months of जीवन और costing only $ 25.
This difference is due to the निम्नतर लागत of स्वास्थ्य care, the निम्नतर लागत of many vaccines provided to विकासशील nations, और that अधिक expensive vaccines, often for less common रोगों, हैं नहीं utilized.
In 1900, the smallpox vaccine was the तभी एक administered to children.
By the जल्दी 1950s, children routinely प्राप्त four vaccines, लिये सुरक्षा against ( diphtheria, pertussis, टेटनस, पोलियो, और smallpox ), और as many as पाँच shots by two सालो of age.
चूंकि the mid-1980s, अनेक vaccines have महरूम added to the अनुसूची.
, the us centers लिये बीमारी कंट्रोल और Prevention ( CDC ) अभी recommends टीकाकरण against at तनिक चौदह रोगों.
By दो सालो of आयु, u.S. children प्राप्त as अनेक as 24 vaccine injections, और might प्राप्त up to five shots दौरान एक visit to the doctor.

The त्रिनिदाद और टोबैगो Carnival is an annual event held on the सोमवार और मंगलवार before राख बुधवार, और is खूब ज्ञात लिये participant 's रंगीन वेशभूषा and exuberant celebrations.
Carnival in Trinidad and टोबैगो is the सबसे significant event on the आइलैंड्स ' cultural और tourism calendar, साथ numerous cultural कार्यक्रम running in the lead up to the गली parade on कार्निवल सोमवार and मंगलवार.
it is कहा कि if the आइलैंडर्स हैं not celebrating it, तब they हैं तैयारी for it, while reminiscing about the past साल 's पर्व.
the दिल of the musical जश्न has been कैलिप्सो ; recently सोका रै replaced कैलिप्सो as the सबसे celebrated प्रकार of music.
वेशभूषा, stickfighting और limbo competitions हैं भी महत्वपूर्ण components of the पर्व.
कार्निवल as it is मनाये in Trinidad और Tobago is भी celebrated in cities विश्वव्यापी.
ये सहित Toronto 's caribana, Miami 's मियामी कार्निवल, ह्यूस्टन carifest, लंदन 's नॉटिंग हिल Carnival as खूब as नई यॉर्क City 's Labor दिन कार्निवल to नाम a few.
Carnival was created when वेस्ट अफ़्रीकी slaves mimicked उनके French स्वामी जो where known for their lavish costumes balls.
हराम to partake in ये festivities and confined to their quarters, slaves संयुक्त elements इससे their अपना संस्कृतियों to उनके निपुण 's fete.
Hence the creation of वर्ण such as jab jab or jab Molassie ( शैतानों ), मध्यरात्रि लुटेरों, imps, Lagahroo, soucouyant, La diablesse और राक्षसों.
साथ the abolition of गुलामी in 1838, freed africans took their संस्करण of कार्निवल to the streets through अभिव्यक्ति of ड्रम, riddim भाग जैसे tamboo बाँसुरी and as प्रत्येक new अप्रवासी जनसांख्यिकी डाला त्रिनिदाद, कार्निवल evolved into कया we जान आज.

He थी inaugurated on May 16, 2011.
`` उत्तेजित up kicks '' is a सोंग by अमरीकी इंडी पॉप बैंड Foster the People.
it was released as the group 's डेब्यू सिंगल in सितंबर 2010, and the following साल थी शामिल on their ep फोस्टर the People और उनके debut एल्बम torches.
`` Pumped Up Kicks '' became the समूह 's breakthrough hit और was one of the most लोकप्रिय गीतों of 2011.

चिहृ with the upbeat musical संयोजन, the lyrics describe the homicidal विचार of a troubled युवावस्था.

the सोंग was widely praised by आलोचकों, and it रै been licensed for use in a चौड़ी range of popular media since इसके रिलीज.

अंतर्गत the संयुक्त राज्य संविधान, the President of the United राज्य is the head of state और सिर of सरकारी of the United States.
As मुख्य of the कार्यपालिका branch और सिर of the संघीय सरकारी as a पूरे, the प्रेसिडेंसी is the highest राजनैतिक office in the United States by influence and मान्यता.
The अध्यक्ष is भी the commander-in-chief of the संयुक्त राज्य हथियारबंद Forces.
the अध्यक्ष is indirectly निर्वाचित to a four-year term by an चुनावी कॉलेज ( or by the हाउस of Representatives should the Electoral College fail to पुरस्कार an absolute majority of मत to कोई व्यक्ति ).
चूंकि the अनुसमर्थन of the Twenty-second Amendment to the United States संविधान in 1951, no person may be निर्वाचित President more than twice, and no एक जो has परोसा अधिक than दो सालो of a पद to जिससे someone else was elected may be निर्वाचित more than once.
Upon the death, इस्तीफा, or हटाना इससे office of an incumbent अध्यक्ष, the वाइस अध्यक्ष assumes the office.
The President जरूर be at तनिक 35 सालो of आयु and a `` प्राकृतिक born '' नागरिक of the United States.
इस list includes only those persons who were sworn into office as अध्यक्ष following the ratification of the United States Constitution, which took प्रभाव on कूच 4, 1789.
लिये American leaders before this अनुसमर्थन, देखिए अध्यक्ष of the Continental कॉंग्रेस.
The सूची करता not शामिल any एक्टिंग Presidents अंतर्गत the twenty-fifth amendment to the United States संविधान.
There have been 43 लोगों sworn into दफ्तर, and 44 presidencies, as ग्रोवर क्लीवलैंड परोसा दो non-consecutive शर्तें and is गिने chronologically as both the 22nd and 24th अध्यक्ष.
Of the individuals elected as president, चार died in दफ्तर of प्राकृतिक causes ( William हेनरी हैरिसन, zachary टेलर, वारेन G. हार्डिंग, और फ्रैंकलिन D. Roosevelt ), four were assassinated ( Abraham lincoln, जेम्स A. गारफ़ील्ड, विलियम mckinley, और जॉन F. Kennedy ) और one resigned ( रिचर्ड Nixon ).
जार्ज वॉशिंगटन, the first president, थी inaugurated in 1789 बाद a सर्वसम्मत vote of the चुनावी कॉलेज.
William हेनरी Harrison खर्च the shortest समय in दफ्तर with 32 days in 1841, और फ्रैंकलिन D. Roosevelt spent the longest साथ over बारह सालो, लकिन died shortly into his चौथी पद in 1945.
he is the तभी अध्यक्ष to serve अधिक than two शर्तें, और a संवैधानिक amendment, affecting presidents बाद Harry ट्रूमैन, was passed to सीमा the number of टाइम्स an individual can be निर्वाचित president.
Andrew Jackson, the सातवाँ president, थी the पहला to be निर्वाचित by men of all वर्ग in 1828 बाद most कानून barring non-land-owners इससे मतदान यहूद repealed.
वारेन Harding थी the पहला elected बाद महिलाओं gained मतदान अधिकारों in 1920.
इतिहास रिकॉर्ड चार presidents – जॉन q एडम्स, Rutherford B. हेज़, बेंजामिन Harrison और जार्ज W. बुश – who खोया the popular vote लकिन assumed दफ्तर.
John F. कैनेडी रै महरूम the तभी अध्यक्ष of रोमन कैथोलिक faith, and the वर्तमान अध्यक्ष, Barack ओबामा, is the first अध्यक्ष of African descent.

the longest unambiguously प्रलेखित इंसान जीवनकाल is कि of jeanne calment of फ़्रांस ( 1875–1997 ), who died at आयु 122 सालो, 164 days.

the प्रणाली has been duplicated by most of the दिखाएँ 's successors in the judicial genre.
Moreover, the People 's अदालत is the first popular, long-running वास्तविकता in the न्यायिक genre.
it was preceded only by a few short-lived हकीकत in the genre ; ये short-lived पूर्ववर्तियों were only loosely सम्बन्धित to न्यायिक proceedings, मगर for एक : पैरोल ( 1959 ) took फुटेज इससे real-life courtrooms holding विधिक कार्यवाही.

This बाएँ the दिखाएँ साथ a कुल of 2,484 1⁄2-hour episodes और 12 सीज़न.

यूटा ( or ) ( Arapaho : wo'tééneihí ' ) is a state in the पश्चिमी United राज्य.
It became the 45th state admitted to the Union on January 4, 1896.
यूटा is the 13th-largest, the 34th-most populous, and the 10th-least-densely populated of the 50 United States.
Approximately 80 % of यूटा 's 2,817,222 लोगों सजीव साथ the wasatch सामने, centering on नमक झील नगर, leaving vast expanses of the state nearly uninhabited और making the population the छठे सबसे urbanized in the U.S. Utah is bordered by Colorado on the ईस्ट, व्योमिंग on the पूर्वोत्तर, idaho on the उत्तर, Arizona on the दक्षिण, and Nevada on the वेस्ट.

the मुश्किल palate is a thin आड़ा bony थाली of the skull, located in the roof of the mouth.
it spans the मेहराब formed by the अपर teeth.
it is formed by the palatine प्रक्रम of the maxilla और आड़ा थाली of palatine अस्थि.
it फ़ॉर्म a विभाजन between the nasal passages and the मुँह.

Complete set of scrolls, constituting the संपूर्ण tanakh.
the tanakh (, or ; भी Tenakh, Tenak, Tanach ) is a नाम used in judaism लिये the canon of the यहूदी बाइबल.
the tanakh is also ज्ञात as the masoretic टेक्स्ट or the miqra.
the नाम is an acronym formed from the आरंभिक Hebrew letters of the Masoretic Text 's three परंपरागत subdivisions : The तोरा ( `` Teaching '', also known as the पाँच Books of Moses ), nevi'im ( `` नबियों '' ) and Ketuvim ( `` कृतियाँ '' ) —hence tanakh.
The name `` miqra '' ( מקרא ), अर्थ `` that which is पढ़ा '', is an वैकल्पिक Hebrew term लिये the Tanakh.
the books of the tanakh were relayed with an accompanying oral परंपरा passed on by प्रत्येक generation, पुकारा the मौखिक तोरा.

ड्राइविंग अंतर्गत the influence ( dui ), ड्राइविंग while intoxicated ( dwi ), drunken ड्राइविंग, नशे ड्राइविंग, drink ड्राइविंग, ऑपरेटिंग अंतर्गत the influence, drinking and driving, or impaired ड्राइविंग is the अपराधों of driving a motor गाडी साथ रक्त levels of दारू in excess of a विधिक सीमा ( `` रक्त Alcohol Content '', or `` bac '' ).
समान regulations cover ड्राइविंग or operating निश्चित types of machinery while प्रभावित by drinking दारू or लेने अन्य drugs, including, but नहीं सीमित to नुस्खा drugs.
This is a दण्ड ठोकर in सबसे राष्ट्र.
convictions do नहीं necessarily involve वास्तविक driving of the vehicle.
In most jurisdictions a measurement such as a blood alcohol सामग्री ( BAC ) in excess of a विशिष्ट threshold level, such as 0.05 % or 0.08 % defines the offense, साथ no need to prove पुतलियों or being अंतर्गत the influence of alcohol.
in some jurisdictions, वहीँ is an क्रोधित श्रेणी of the ठोकर at a higher level e.g. 0.12 %.
in सबसे countries, anyone who is convicted of injuring or हत्या किसी जबकि under the influence of दारू or दवाएँ can be heavily fined, as in फ़्रांस, in जोड to being दिए a lengthy थाना वाक्य.
कुछ jobs have उनके अपना rules और bac हद, लिये उदाहरण वाणिज्यिक पायलट, और the संघीय रेलरोड प्रशासन in the United राज्य has a 0.04 % सीमा लिये train क्रू.
कुछ jurisdictions have multiple levels of BAC ; लिये example, the state of कैलिफ़ोर्निया रै a 0.08 % bac सीमा, which is lowered to 0.04 % if the operator holds a वाणिज्यिक ड्राइवर 's license.
the कैलिफ़ोर्निया BAC सीमा is 0.01 % for those younger than 21 years of age और those on probation लिये a previous DUI conviction.
Some विशाल corporations have उनके अपना नियम ; Union Pacific Railroad रै उनके अपना BAC सीमा of 0.02 % कि, if violated during a random परीक्षण or a for-cause test — for उदाहरण, after a ट्रैफ़िक दुर्घटना — can परिणाम in termination of नियुक्ति साथ no chance of भविष्य re-hire.
अनेक states in the u.S. और provinces in कनाडा have अपनाया सच्चाई in sentencing कानून कि enforce सख्त दिशानिर्देश on sentencing, differing इससे पिछला practice जहाँ थाना time थी घटाया or निलंबित बाद sentencing had महरूम issued.
कुछ jurisdictions have न्यायिक guidelines requiring a अनिवार्य न्यूनतम sentence.
Penalties लिये dui आरोप दायरा इससे महंगी शुल्क to forfetiruree of your अनुज्ञा plates और in कुछ serious circumstances, your गाडी.

the विशिष्ट criminal ठोकर may be called, depending on the क्षेत्राधिकार, driving अंतर्गत the influence [ of दारू or other drugs ] ( dui ), driving under intense influence ( duii ), ड्राइविंग जबकि intoxicated ( DWI ), ऑपरेटिंग under the influence ( oui ) ऑपरेटिंग जबकि intoxicated ( OWI ), ऑपरेटिंग a motor गाडी जबकि intoxicated ( OMVI ), ड्राइविंग अंतर्गत the संयुक्त influence of alcohol and/or अन्य drugs, ड्राइविंग अंतर्गत the influence प्रति se or नशे in charge [ of a vehicle ].
अनेक such laws लागू also to motorcycling, boating, piloting वायुयान, use of motile फार्म equipment ऐसे as tractors and combines, सवारी घोड़े or ड्राइविंग a horse-drawn गाडी, or bicycling, संभवतः साथ अलग bac level than driving.
in कुछ jurisdictions वहीँ हैं पृथक charges depending on the vehicle प्रयुक्त, ऐसे as BWI ( bicycling जबकि intoxicated ), which may carry a हल्का वाक्य.
In the United राज्य, local law enforcement एजेंसियों बना 1,467,300 रखवाले nationwide for ड्राइविंग अंतर्गत the influence of alcohol in 1996, compared to 1.9 लाख ऐसे रखवाले during the शिखर साल in 1983.

Law प्रवर्तन in the संयुक्त राज्य is one of तीन प्रमुख components of the criminal justice system of the United राज्य, साथ with न्यायालयों और corrections.
हालांकि there exists an inherent interrelatedness between the अलग समूह that make up the criminal इंसाफ प्रणाली आधारित on उनके अपराधों deterrence purpose, each घटक operates independently इससे one another.
However, the न्यायपालिका is vested साथ the शक्ति to मेक विधिक determinations regarding the conduct of the अन्य दो components.
अलावा from maintaining order and service कृत्यों, the purpose of policing is the investigation of suspected criminal कार्यकलाप और the referral of the results of investigations and of suspected अपराधियों to the courts.
Law प्रवर्तन, to varying डिग्री at different स्तर of सरकारी and in अलग एजेंसियों, is also commonly चार्ज साथ the जिम्मेदारियों of deterring दण्ड activity और of preventing the कामयाब commission of अपराधों in प्रगति ; the service और प्रवर्तन of वारंट, writs और अन्य आदेश of the न्यायालयों.
विधि प्रवर्तन एजेंसियों हैं also शामिल in providing first जवाब to emergencies और अन्य threats to पब्लिक safety ; the protection of certain पब्लिक सुविधाएं और infrastructure ; the मेंटेनेंस of पब्लिक अनुक्रम ; the protection of पब्लिक officials ; और the operation of कुछ correctional सुविधाएं ( usually at the local level ).

an Academy पुरस्कार -winner, वेन was among the शीर्ष box दफ्तर draws for three दशकों, और was नामित the all-time शीर्ष money-making स्टार.

Wayne was born in Winterset, Iowa लकिन his family relocated to the वृहद Los Angeles क्षेत्रफल when he थी four years बूढ़ा.

Galileo Galilei ( ; 15 February 1564 – 8 January 1642 ), was an इतालवी physicist, गणितज्ञ, astronomer, और philosopher जो played a प्रमुख role in the Scientific क्रान्ति.
उसके उपलब्धियाँ include सुधार to the दूरदर्शी और consequent astronomical observations और support for copernicanism.
Galileo has महरूम पुकारा the `` पिता of modern observational astronomy ``, the `` father of आधुनिक physics ``, the `` पिता of विज्ञान '', और `` the पिता of आधुनिक विज्ञान ''.
His योगदान to observational खगोलशास्त्र शामिल the telescopic पुष्टि of the phases of Venus, the डिस्कवरी of the चार largest satellites of बृहस्पति ( नामित the galilean moons in उसके इज्ज़त ), और the अवलोकन और analysis of sunspots.
गैलीलियो भी worked in लागू विज्ञान और प्रौद्योगिकी, inventing an improved military कम्पास और अन्य यंत्र.
गैलीलियो 's championing of heliocentrism थी विवादास्पद भीतर उसके आजीवन, जब most subscribed to either geocentrism or the Tychonic system.
he met with विपक्ष from खगोलशास्त्रियों, जो doubted heliocentrism due to the अनुपस्थिति of an observed तारकीय लंबन.
the पदार्थ was investigated by the रोमन Inquisition in 1615, and they concluded कि it could be समर्थित as only a सम्भावना, नहीं an established fact.
गैलीलियो later defended his दृश्य in संवाद Concerning the दो Chief World प्रणालियों, जिससे appeared to attack पोप शहरी VIII and यूँ alienated उसे and the Jesuits, who had दोनो supported गैलीलियो up जबतक इस पाइंट.
He थी tried by the Inquisition, found `` ओजस्वी suspect of heresy '', मजबूर to recant, और खर्च the rest of उसके life अंतर्गत house arrest.
It थी जबकि Galileo was under हाउस गिरफ़्तार कि he wrote one of उसके finest works, दो New Sciences, in जिससे he summarised the work he था किया some forty सालो earlier, on the दो sciences अभी called kinematics और strength of सामग्री.

demonstration of a लचीली oled यंत्र
an oled ( organic light-emitting डायोड ) is a light-emitting डायोड ( led ) in जिससे the emissive electroluminescent layer is a फिल्मी of organic यौगिक जिससे emits light in जवाब to an इलेक्ट्रिक वर्तमान.
इस परत of सशुल्क सेमीकंडक्टर is situated between दो electrodes.
generally, at तनिक one of these electrodes is transparent.
OLEDs are used to बनाएँ digital प्रदर्शक in डिवाइस such as टेलीविज़न screens, computer monitors, पोर्टेबल प्रणालियों such as मोबाईल फोन, हैंडहेल्ड खेल consoles और PDAs.
a प्रमुख area of research is the development of white oled डिवाइस लिये उपयोग in solid-state lighting अनुप्रयोग.
वहीँ हैं दो प्रमुख परिवारों of oleds : those आधारित on छोटी अणुओं और those employing polymers.
adding मोबाईल ions to an OLED creates a light-emitting electrochemical कोशिका or LEC, जिससे रै a थोड़ा different विधि of आपरेशन.
oled प्रदर्शक can उपयोग either passive-matrix ( pmoled ) or active-matrix addressing schemes.
active-matrix OLEDs ( amoled ) आवश्यकता a thin-film ट्रांजिस्टर backplane to स्विच प्रत्येक individual पिक्सेल on or बंद, but allow for higher रेज़ोल्यूशन और larger display आकार.
An oled प्रदर्शक works without a backlight.
यूँ, it can display deep ब्लैक स्तर और can be thinner और lighter than a द्रव crystal प्रदर्शक ( एलसीडी ).
In कम परिवेश light conditions such as a dark room an oled स्क्रीन can achieve a उच्चतर contrast ratio than an LCD, whether the एलसीडी उपयोग ठंडा cathode fluorescent lamps or led backlight.
a carton और a कांच of eggnog from Montreal, Canada, प्रर्दशित इसके French मुखाग्र ( English रिवर्स ) और the French पद लेत de poule ( वस्तुतः, `` मुर्गी 's मिल्क '' )
eggnog, or अंडा nog, is a sweetened दुग्ध -आधारd पेय traditionally बना with मिल्क and/or मलाई, sugar, and whipped अंडे ( which देता it a frothy texture ).
ब्रांडी, rum, व्हिस्की, bourbon, वोदका, or a संयोजन of liquors are often added.
The समाप्त सेवारत is प्रायः garnished साथ a sprinkling of मैदान दालचीनी or nutmeg.
It थी भी ज्ञात as the egg मिल्क punch.
Eggnog is a popular पेय throughout the United राज्य and कनाडा, and is प्रायः associated साथ Christmas.
eggnog may be added as a flavoring to खाना or पेय such as कॉफी और चाय.
Eggnog as a कस्टर्ड can also be प्रयुक्त as an ice cream आधार.
a pasty (, ), ( sometimes ज्ञात in Britain as a Cornish pasty, and in the संयुक्त States as a pastie or अंग्रेजों pasty ) is a baked pastry, a traditional किस्में of जिससे is विशेषकर संबद्ध साथ कॉर्नवॉल, the westernmost काउंटी in इंग्लैण्ड.
it is made by रखकर uncooked भरना typically of meat and सब्जियां, without मांस in शाकाहारी versions, on a flat पेस्ट्री वृत्त और फोल्डिंग it to wrap the भरना, crimping the edge to रूप a मुहर.
बाद बेकिंग, the result is a उठाया semicircular comestible.
the परंपरागत cornish pasty, जिससे रै सुरक्षित भौगोलिक indication ( pgi ) औकात in यूरोपीय, is filled with beef, sliced or diced potato, swede ( भी ज्ञात as a पीला turnip or rutabaga – referred to in Cornwall as शलजम ) and प्याज, seasoned साथ salt और pepper, and is baked.
Today, the pasty is the खाना सबसे associated with Cornwall, it is regarded as the नेशनल डिश, और it खाते for 6 % of the cornish खाना economy.
Pasties साथ many different fillings हैं बना ; कुछ दुकानें specialise in selling all sorts of pasties.
the origins of the pasty हैं unclear, though there are many सन्दर्भ to them throughout historical documents और fiction.
the pasty is अभी लोकप्रिय world-wide due to the स्प्रेड of Cornish miners, और विसंगतियाँ can be मिला in ऑस्ट्रेलिया, the संयुक्त States, Mexico and elsewhere.
the ( ortho- ) सहानुभूतिपूर्ण बेचैन system ( sns ) is एक of three प्रमुख parts of the autonomic बेचैन system : the अन्य being the enteric and parasympathetic systems.
Its सामान्य कार्रवाई is to mobilize the देह 's nervous प्रणाली fight-or-flight response.
it is, however, constantly active at a basic स्तर to maintain homeostasis.
सुरक्षित Digital or ( sd ) is a non-volatile memory card स्वरूप for उपयोग in पोर्टेबल devices, ऐसे as mobile phones, डिजिटल कैमरे, gps navigation devices, and टैब्लेट कंप्यूटर.
The Secure Digital मानक is कायम by the sd Card संघ ( sda ).
sd technologies have महरूम implemented in more than 400 brands आरपार dozens of उत्पाद categories और अधिक than 8,000 मॉडल.
the सुरक्षित डिजिटल format includes four card परिवारों उपलब्धियाँ in तीन अलग form factors.
the four परिवारों are the original standard-capacity ( sdsc ), the high-capacity ( sdhc ), the eXtended-Capacity ( sdxc ), और the SDIO, which combines input/output कृत्यों साथ data storage.
the three form कारकों हैं the असली आकार, the `` मिनी '' size, and the `` सूक्ष्म '' आकार ( देखिए उदाहरण ).
वहीँ are अनेक combinations of रूप factors and यंत्र families.
Electrically passive adapters allow the उपयोग of a छोटी कार्ड in a host device built to थाम a larger card.
मेजबान डिवाइस that comply साथ नए संस्करण of the specification provide backward संगतता और accept older sd ताश, but इस आलेख explains several कारकों that can prevent the उपयोग of a newer SD card:
A नए card may प्रस्ताव greater capacity than the मेजबान device can हैंडल.
A नए card may उपयोग a संचिका प्रणाली the मेजबान device can नहीं navigate.
Use of an SDIO कार्ड requires the मेजबान यंत्र be designed for the input/output कृत्यों the कार्ड provides.
the organization of the कार्ड was changed starting साथ the SDHC परिवार.
कुछ विक्रेता उत्पादित sdsc ताश ऊपर 1 gb before the SDA था standardized a विधि of doing so.
the sda उपयोग several trademarked लोगो to enforce compliance with इसके specifications और assure उपयोक्ता of संगतता.

Daniel लॉरेंस व्हिटनी ( born फ़रवरी 17, 1963 ) best known by उसके स्टेज नाम और अक्षर लैरी the Cable Guy, is an American stand-up comedian, कर्ता, देश म्यूज़िक artist, voice actor, and पूर्व रेडियो व्यक्तित्व.

Vitamin d is a group of fat-soluble secosteroids जिम्मेदार लिये intestinal अवशोषण of कैल्सियम and फास्फेट.
In इंसानो, the सबसे महत्वपूर्ण related यौगिकों of विटामिन D are विटामिन D2 and vitamin D3.
cholecalciferol ( vitamin d3 ) और ergocalciferol ( विटामिन D2 ) are unique as वे constitute what we जान as विटामिन d और can be ingested इससे the आहार and/or पूरक.
the देह can भी synthesize विटामिन d ( इससे cholesterol ) when सूर्य exposure is adequate ( hence its उपनाम, the `` sunshine vitamin '' ).
हालांकि विटामिन d is commonly called a विटामिन, it is not दरअसल an essential dietary vitamin in the strict sense, as it can be synthesized in पर्याप्त amounts by most स्तनधारियों उजागर to sunlight.
( Cats और dogs can नहीं synthesize विटामिन d efficiently and must प्राप्त it in उनके आहार. )
An सशुल्क chemical यौगिक ( or सम्बन्धित नियत of यौगिकों ) is only scientifically पुकारा a vitamin when it can not be synthesized in sufficient quantities by an सजीव, and must be obtained from their आहार.
However, as with अन्य compounds commonly पुकारा vitamins, विटामिन D was खोजा in an प्रयत्न to find the dietary पदार्थ कि थी lacking in a बीमारी, namely, rickets, the childhood form of osteomalacia.
additionally, like अन्य compounds पुकारा विटामिन, in the developed world विटामिन D is added to स्टेपल भोजन, such as मिल्क, to avoid बीमारी due to deficiency.
Measures of सीरम levels reflect endogenous संश्लेषण from exposure to धूप as खूब as सेवन from the आहार, और it is believed कि संश्लेषण may contribute generally to the maintenance of पर्याप्त सीरम concentrations.
the evidence indicates कि the संश्लेषण of विटामिन d from सूर्य exposure works in a प्रतिक्रिया लूप that रोकता toxicity लकिन, क्युकी of अनिश्चितता परिचय the कर्कट risk from धूप, no सुझाव are जारी by the Institute of आयुर्विज्ञान, USA, for the राशि of सूर्य exposure जरूरी to meet विटामिन d requirements.
तदनुसार, the Dietary सन्दर्भ Intakes लिये विटामिन d assume that no संश्लेषण occurs और that सब of a person 's विटामिन d is from their आहार, although कि होगा rarely occur in अभ्यास.
In the जिगर विटामिन D is परिवर्तित to calcidiol, which is also known as calcifediol ( इन ), 25-hydroxycholecalciferol, or 25-hydroxyvitamin D—abbreviated 25 ( oh ) d ; and जिससे is the विशिष्ट विटामिन D metabolite कि is measured in सीरम to determine a person 's विटामिन d औकात.
Part of the calcidiol is परिवर्तित by the kidneys to calcitriol, the biologically active रूप of विटामिन D. calcitriol circulates as a hormone in the blood, regulating the विशेषज्ञता of कैल्सियम और फास्फेट in the bloodstream और promoting the स्वस्थ विकास और remodeling of bone.
calcidiol is also परिवर्तित to calcitriol outside of the गुर्दे for other उद्देश्य, ऐसे as the proliferation, differentiation and apoptosis of cells ; calcitriol also affects neuromuscular फलन and inflammation.
Beyond इसके use to prevent osteomalacia or rickets, the evidence लिये अन्य स्वास्थ्य प्रभाव of विटामिन D supplementation in the general population is असंगत.
the best evidence of लाभ is लिये अस्थि स्वास्थ्य and a घटी in मृत्यु in elderly महिलाओं.
मानक रूप of the आवधिक table.
The colors represent अलग श्रेणी of elements समझाया below.
The आवधिक table is a table display of the रासायनिक तत्व, organized on the आधार of their परमाणु संख्याएँ, इलेक्ट्रॉन configurations, और पुनरावर्ती रासायनिक गुण.
तत्व हैं presented in अनुक्रम of increasing परमाणु क्रमांक ( क्रमांक of protons ).
The standard रूप of तालिका comprises an 18 × 7 ग्रिड or main body of elements, positioned ऊपर a छोटी double पंक्ति of elements.
the तालिका can भी be deconstructed into four rectangular ब्लॉक : the s-block to the left, the p-block to the right, the d-block in the middle, और the f-block नीचे that.
the पंक्ति of the table are called अवधि ; the कालम of the s-, d-, and p-blocks हैं called groups, साथ some of ये having names such as the हैलोजन्स or the प्रतिष्ठित गैसों.
चूंकि, by definition, a आवधिक तालिका incorporates पुनरावर्ती रुझान, कोई such तालिका can be used to derive relationships between the properties of the elements and भविष्यवाणी the properties of new, yet to be खोजा or synthesized, तत्व.
As a result, a आवधिक table—whether in the मानक form or some अन्य variant—provides a उपयोगी framework लिये analyzing रासायनिक बर्ताव, और ऐसे tables हैं widely प्रयुक्त in रसायन और अन्य sciences.
हालांकि precursors मौजूद, dmitri mendeleev is generally credited with the publication, in 1869, of the पहला widely recognized periodic table.
He विकसित उसके table to illustrate periodic रुझान in the properties of the then-known तत्व.
Mendeleev भी predicted some properties of then-unknown elements that होता be अपेक्षित to भरण गैप in इस table.
Most of उसके पूर्वानुमान were proved सही जब the तत्व in सवाल यहूद subsequently discovered.
Mendeleev 's आवधिक तालिका has चूंकि been विस्तारित and refined with the डिस्कवरी or synthesis of further नई तत्व और the development of नई theoretical मॉडल to बताइये रासायनिक बर्ताव.
All elements from परमाणु numbers 1 ( हाइड्रोजन ) to 118 ( ununoctium ) have महरूम खोजा or synthesized.
The elements इससे 1 to 98 ( californium ) have been मिला to मौजूद naturally, although some हैं found only in trace amounts और यहूद initially खोजा by synthesis in laboratories.
the तत्व बाद 98 have तभी been synthesized in laboratories.
उत्पादन of तत्व beyond ununoctium is होने धड़ा, साथ the सवाल of कैसा the periodic table may need to be modified to accommodate any such additions होने a पदार्थ of जारी बहस.
numerous synthetic radionuclides of naturally occurring तत्व have also महरूम उत्पादित in laboratories.

in the संयुक्त राज्य, workers हैं generally हकदार to be सशुल्क no less than the statutory न्यूनतम मजदूरी.

bourbon whiskey is a प्रकार of अमरीकी whiskey – a barrel-aged आसुत स्पिरिट made primarily from मकई.

The mona लिसा ( La gioconda or la joconde ) is a half-length portrait of a woman by the इतालवी कलाकार लियोनार्डो da विंची, which रै been acclaimed as `` the best known, the सबसे visited, the सबसे written परिचय, the सबसे सुंग परिचय, the सबसे parodied work of art in the world. ''
the पेंटिंग, विचार to be a पोर्ट्रेट of Lisa Gherardini, the wife of francesco डेल Giocondo, is in आयल on a poplar panel, and is believed to have महरूम चित्रित between 1503 और 1506.
it was acquired by किंग Francis i of France and is now the प्रॉपर्टी of the फ्रेंच Republic, on permanent प्रदर्शक at the musée du louvre in पेरिस since 1797.
The ambiguity of the subject 's अभिव्यक्ति, जिससे is अक्सर described as enigmatic, the monumentality of the composition, the हल्का मॉडलिंग of forms and the वायुमंडलीय illusionism यहूद अनोखा qualities that have contributed to the continuing fascination और पढ़ाई of the work.

prise de la bastille by Jean-Pierre-Louis-Laurent houel
Bastille दिन is the नाम given in english-speaking countries to the फ्रेंच नेशनल दिन, which is मनाये on the 14th of July प्रत्येक year.
In France, it is formally पुकारा la Fête nationale ( ; The नेशनल Celebration ) और commonly le quatorze juillet ( ; the fourteenth of जुलाई ).
it commemorates the 1790 fête de la fédération, held on the first anniversary of the storming of the bastille on 14 जुलाई 1789 ; the वर्षगांठ of the storming of the Bastille fortress-prison थी seen as a प्रतीक of the uprising of the आधुनिक nation, and of the reconciliation of all the French inside the संवैधानिक monarchy जिससे preceded the पहला गणतंत्र, during the French Revolution.
festivities और आधिकारिक ceremonies हैं held all over France.
the oldest and largest regular सैन्य परेड in यूरोपीय is आयोजित on the morning of 14 July, on the champs-élysées एवेन्यू in Paris in सामने of the अध्यक्ष of the गणतंत्र, French officials और विदेशी guests.
the United राज्य of अमेरिका ( यूएसए or u.s.A. ), commonly पुकारा the United राज्य ( US or u.S. ) or America, is a federal गणतंत्र consisting of fifty राज्य और a संघीय ज़िला.
The lower forty-eight संलग्न राज्य और the संघीय ज़िला of वॉशिंगटन, d.C. are in सेंट्रल उत्तर America between कनाडा and Mexico.
the राज्य of अलास्का is west of कनाडा and east of रूस across the बेरिंग जलसन्धि, और the राज्य of Hawaii is in the mid-north प्रशांत.
the country भी रै पाँच आबादी and nine unpopulated territories in the Pacific और the Caribbean.
at 3.79 million वर्गाकार miles ( 9.83 लाख km2 ) and साथ around 315 million people, the संयुक्त States is the third- or fourth-largest देश by कुल क्षेत्रफल और the third-largest by दोनो land area और population.
it is one of the संसार 's most ethnically diverse और multicultural राष्ट्र, the उत्पाद of large-scale आव्रजन इससे अनेक देशों.
The भूगोल और जलवायु of the U.S. is भी extremely विविध, साथ deserts, plains, forests, और kyu कि हैं home to a चौड़ी किस्में of species.
Paleoindians migrated from एशिया to कया is now the संयुक्त राज्य mainland around 15,000 years ago.
बाद 1500, बूढ़ा World diseases introduced by Europeans greatly घटाया उनके populations.
European colonization began around 1600 and came ज़्यादातर from इंग्लैण्ड.
The संयुक्त राज्य उभरा from तेरह अंग्रेजों colonies located along the Atlantic seaboard.
विवादों between Great ब्रिटेन और the अमरीकी colonies led to the American क्रान्ति.
On July 4, 1776, delegates from the 13 colonies unanimously जारी the घोषणा of Independence, जिससे स्थापित the United States of अमेरिका.
The American क्रांतिकारी War, which ended साथ the recognition of independence of the United राज्य इससे the किंगडम of ग्रेट Britain, थी the first successful war of स्वतंत्रता विरूद्ध a European colonial empire.
The वर्तमान Constitution was अपनाया on सितंबर 17, 1787 ; twenty-seven Amendments have चूंकि been added to the संविधान.
the पहला टेन amendments, collectively नामित the विधेयक of अधिकारों, were ratified in 1791 and गारंटी अनेक fundamental civil अधिकारों और freedoms.
चलित by the doctrine of manifest नियति, the United राज्य embarked on a vigorous विस्तार आरपार North America throughout the 19th सदी.

the American सिविल War ended legalized गुलामी in the संयुक्त States.

the ncaa मेन 's Division i बास्केट Championship is a single-elimination टूर्नामेंट निभाई प्रत्येक spring in the संयुक्त States, currently featuring 68 कॉलेज बास्केट टीमों, to determine the नेशनल चैंपियनशिप of the प्रमुख कॉलेज बास्केट टीमों.
the टूर्नामेंट, organized by the National Collegiate एथलेटिक Association ( NCAA ), was निर्मित दौरान 1939 by the नेशनल Association of बास्केट Coaches, and was the विचार of ओहियो State विश्वविद्यालयों coach Harold olsen.
निभाई ज़्यादातर during March, it is known informally as March Madness or the बिग नृत्य, और has become एक of the सबसे famous सालाना sporting कार्यक्रम in the संयुक्त राज्य.
The NCAA रै credited Bob वाल्श of the सिएटल आयोजन कमेटी for starting the March दीवानगी जश्न दौरान 1984.
The टूर्नामेंट टीमों include champions from 31 प्रभाग i सम्मेलनों ( which प्राप्त स्वचालित bids ), और 37 teams जिससे हैं awarded at-large berths.
ये `` at-large '' टीमों are chosen by an NCAA selection कमेटी, as detailed below.
The 64 teams are विभाजित into four regions और organized into a single विलोपन `` कोष्ठक '', जिससे predetermines, जब a team विन्स a खेल, which टोली it will face अगला.
प्रत्येक टोली is `` seeded '', or क्रमित, भीतर its प्रदेश.
बाद an आरंभिक four खेल between आठ lower-ranked teams, the टूर्नामेंट occurs during the course of तीन weekends, at pre-selected न्यूट्रल साइट around the संयुक्त राज्य.
Lower-ranked teams are placed in the bracket विरूद्ध उच्चतर क्रमित टीमों.
प्रत्येक weekend eliminates three-fourths of the टीमों, इससे a गोलाकार of 64, to a `` मीठी Sixteen '', और लिये the पिछला वीकेंड of the टूर्नामेंट a फाइनल Four ; the Final Four is usually निभाई during the पहला वीकेंड of April.
ये चार teams, एक इससे प्रत्येक प्रदेश, then compete in एक स्थान लिये the national चैंपियनशिप.

a नमूना of सिंथेटिक motor oil
Synthetic आयल is a lubricant consisting of रासायनिक यौगिकों कि हैं artificially बना ( synthesized ).
Synthetic lubricants can be manufactured using chemically परिवर्धित petroleum components rather than whole crude आयल, लकिन can also be synthesized इससे अन्य raw सामग्री.
Synthetic आयल is प्रयुक्त as a स्थानापन्न लिये स्नेहक परिष्कृत from पेट्रोलियम जब ऑपरेटिंग in extremes of तापमान, क्युकी, in सामान्य, it provides श्रेष्ठ mechanical and chemical गुण than those मिला in परंपरागत खनिज oils.
Aircraft jet इंजन, for उदाहरण, आवश्यकता the उपयोग of सिंथेटिक oils, whereas वायुयान piston engines do नहीं.

The दिखाएँ थी a hit and lasted नौ सीज़न, इससे 1988 to 1997.
She जीती दोनो an एमी और a Golden ग्लोब पुरस्कार for Best Actress for her कार्य on the show.

francesco Albani 's 17th सदी बपतिस्मा of Christ is a ठेठ depiction साथ the आसमान खोलने and the Holy स्पिरिट descending as a dove.
the baptism of Jesus marks the beginning of उसके पब्लिक मंत्रालय.
This इवेंट is अंकित in the canonical gospels of मैथ्यू, चिह्नित और ल्यूक.
जॉन 's इन्जील does नहीं describe Jesus ' baptism, लकिन जॉन the बैपटिस्ट करता गवाही of the other बाते in.
in the New वसीयत, John the Baptist preached the baptism of repentance लिये the remission of sins ( ), और घोषित खुद a forerunner of he that would baptize `` साथ the पावन भुत और साथ fire '' ( ).
In so doing he was preparing the रास्ता लिये Jesus.
Jesus आए to the जॉर्डन नदी जहाँ he was baptized by John.
the baptismal झाँकी शामिल the आकाश खोलने, a dove-like descent of the Holy स्पिरिट, और a आवाज़ इससे स्वर्ग saying, `` इस is my beloved बेटे, in whom I am खूब pleased. ''
Most आधुनिक विद्वानों view the फैक्ट कि Jesus was baptized by John as an ऐतिहासिक इवेंट to जिससे a ऊँची उपाधि of certainty can be आबंटित.
Along साथ the crucifixion of यीशु most scholars view it as one of the दो historically निश्चित तथ्य about him, and often उपयोग it as the starting अंक for the study of the ऐतिहासिक यीशु.
the बपतिस्मा is एक of the पाँच major माइलस्टोन in the इन्जील कथा of the जीवन of यीशु, the अन्य होने the Transfiguration, crucifixion, क़यामत, और Ascension.
सबसे Christian denominations दृश्य the बपतिस्मा of Jesus as an महत्वपूर्ण इवेंट and a basis लिये the ईसाई रीति of baptism ( देखिए also ).
In पूर्वी Christianity, यीशु ' बपतिस्मा is commemorated on 6 January, the feast of Epiphany.
in the Roman Catholic Church, the anglican नियाज़, the लूथरन चर्च and कुछ अन्य पश्चिमी denominations, it is recalled on a day within the following सप्ताह, the feast of the baptism of the Lord.
In Roman catholicism, the बपतिस्मा of यीशु is one of the चमकदार रहस्यों sometimes added to the rosary.
it is a Trinitarian feast in the पूर्वी Orthodox चर्च.
methylcobalamin ( shown ) is a form of विटामिन B12.
Physically it resembles the अन्य फ़ॉर्म of विटामिन b12, occurring as dark red crystals कि freely रूप cherry-colored पारदर्शी समाधान in water.
Vitamin b12, विटामिन b12 or vitamin b-12, भी called cobalamin, is a water-soluble विटामिन with a कुंजी role in the सामान्य functioning of the दिमाग और बेचैन प्रणाली, and for the formation of रक्त.
it is one of the eight B विटामिन.
it is normally involved in the चयापचय of every कोशिका of the इंसान body, especially affecting डीएनए synthesis and विनियमन, but भी वसीय एसिड synthesis और उर्जा उत्पादन.
neither fungi, plants, nor पशु are सक्षम of producing vitamin B12.
Only bacteria और आर्किया have the enzymes required for इसके संश्लेषण, हालांकि many foods हैं a प्राकृतिक सोर्स of B12 because of bacterial symbiosis.
The विटामिन is the largest and most structurally जटिल विटामिन and can be produced industrially तभी through bacterial fermentation-synthesis.
विटामिन b12 consists of a क्लास of chemically सम्बन्धित यौगिकों ( vitamers ), सब of which have विटामिन activity.
It contains the biochemically विरल तत्व कोबाल्ट.
Biosynthesis of the मौलिक ढांचा of the vitamin is accomplished तभी by bacteria ( which usually produce hydroxocobalamin ), but परिवर्तन between different फ़ॉर्म of the विटामिन can be accomplished in the इंसान देह.
A common semi-synthetic रूप of the विटामिन, cyanocobalamin, करता not occur in nature, लकिन is produced इससे bacterial hydroxocobalamin and then used in many pharmaceuticals और पूरक, और as a food योगात्मक, because of इसके stability और निम्नतर production cost.
In the body it is converted to the human physiological forms methylcobalamin and adenosylcobalamin, leaving पीछे the साइनाइड, albeit in minimal विशेषज्ञता.
अधिक recently, hydroxocobalamin, methylcobalamin, and adenosylcobalamin can be मिला in अधिक महंगी pharmacological उत्पाद और खाना पूरक.
the अतिरिक्त utility of ये is फिलहाल debated.
विटामिन b12 थी discovered from its relationship to the disease घातक रक्ताल्पता, जिससे is an असंक्राम्य बीमारी in which parietal कोशिकाएं of the पेट responsible for secreting intrinsic फ़ैक्टर हैं destroyed.
मूलभूत फ़ैक्टर is crucial लिये the सामान्य अवशोषण of b12, so a कमी of intrinsic फ़ैक्टर, as seen in घातक रक्ताल्पता, causes a विटामिन b12 deficiency.
अनेक अन्य subtler kinds of vitamin B12 कमियां और their biochemical effects have since महरूम elucidated.

चीख 3 is a 2000 American slasher फिल्मी निर्मित by केविन विलियमसन, निर्देशित by Wes craven और लिखा by ehren Kruger, starring Neve कैम्पबेल, courteney कॉक्स Arquette और David arquette.
it थी released on फ़रवरी 4, 2000 as the third installment in the चीख फिल्मी श्रेणी.
the कार्यक्रम of the story are set तीन सालो after those of Scream 2 and follows sidney प्रेस्कॉट ( कैम्पबेल ) who रै gone into self-imposed isolation following the events of the पिछला दो films लकिन is drawn to हॉलीवुड बाद a new Ghostface begins killing the डाल of the फिल्मी भीतर a फिल्मी `` stab 3 ''.
चीख 3 combines the हिंसा of the slasher विधा with कॉमेडी और `` whodunit `` रहस्य while satirizing the cliché of फिल्मी trilogies.
नापसंद the previous Scream films, there थी an increased जोर on comedic elements and the violence और horror was घटाया in response to increased पब्लिक scrutiny about violence in media following the Columbine ऊँची School नरसंहार.
The फिल्मी थी the concluding अध्याय of the Scream श्रेणी until it was revived साथ a sequel, चीख 4, in 2011.
Williamson provided a five-page रूपरेखा लिये दो सिक्वेल to Scream जब auctioning his असली script, उम्मीद to entice bidders साथ the संभावित of खरीदे a मताधिकार.
विलियमसन 's commitments to other प्रोजेक्ट meant he was असमर्थ to develop a पूरा स्क्रिप्ट लिये Scream 3 और writing कर्तव्य यहूद undertaken by Ehren Kruger who discarded much of विलियमसन 's notes.
Craven और मार्को beltrami लौटे to direct and स्कोर the film क्रमशः as they था साथ the previous दो series entries.
Production थी troubled साथ स्क्रिप्ट rewrites, साथ pages sometimes तभी तैयार on the day of फिल्मांकन, और scheduling difficulties with the main डाल.
चीख 3 performed दोनो financially और critically बदतर than इसके preceding films, earning over $ 161 लाख and साथ अनेक आलोचकों claiming कि the film था become what चीख originally `` spoofed ``.
Despite negative criticism the film did प्राप्त तारीफ़ साथ reviewers कॉलिंग it the पूर्ण समाप्त to the चीख त्रयी.

The colonial history of the संयुक्त States कवर the history of यूरोपीय settlements from the start of colonization of America जबतक their incorporation into the United States.
in the लेट 16th century, England, France, स्पेन और the नीदरलैंड्स launched major colonization कार्यक्रम in eastern North अमेरिका.
छोटी early attempts—such as the अंग्रेज़ी खोया Colony of Roanoke —often disappeared ; everywhere the मौत रेट of the पहला आमद थी बहुत high.
Nevertheless कामयाब colonies यहूद स्थापित.
यूरोपीय settlers came इससे a किस्में of social और धार्मिक समूह.
No aristocrats settled permanently, but a क्रमांक of adventurers, सैनिको, किसानो, और tradesmen arrived.
Diversity थी an अमरीकी characteristic as the डच of नई netherland, the swedes और finns of नई स्वीडन, the English Quakers of पेन्सिलवेनिया, the English Puritans of New इंग्लैण्ड, the अंग्रेज़ी settlers of Jamestown, and the `` worthy poor '' of जॉर्जिया, आए to the new महाद्वीप और निर्मित colonies with distinctive social, धार्मिक, political और आर्थिक शैलियाँ.
occasionally एक colony took कंट्रोल of another ( during युद्धों between उनके European parents ).
तभी in Nova स्कोटिया ( now part of Canada ) किया the conquerors निकाल the पिछला colonists.
Instead they सब lived side by पक्ष in सलाम.
There यहूद no major civil युद्धों among the 13 colonies, और the two मुख्य armed विद्रोहों ( in वर्जिनिया in 1676 और in नई यॉर्क in 1689–91 ) यहूद short-lived असफलताओं.
Wars between the फ्रेंच और the British—the French और Indian युद्धों and पिता Rale 's युद्ध —were तूल, and involved French-support लिये wabanaki confederacy हमले on the frontiers.
by 1760 फ़्रांस was पराजित और the British जब्त इसके colonies.
The चार distinct regions यहूद : New इंग्लैण्ड, the Middle colonies, the chesapeake खाड़ी Colonies ( अपर South ) और the निम्नतर South.
कुछ historians add a पांचवां region, the frontier, which was never separately organized.
By the समय यूरोपीय settlers arrived around 1600–1650, the बहुमत of the देशी अमेरिकी living in the पूर्वी संयुक्त राज्य had been decimated by new diseases, introduced to them decades before by explorers और sailors.
