बियोवुल्फ़ ( ; बूढ़ा अंग्रेज़ी : ) is a legendary Geatish hero and बाद turned किंग in the epic कविता named बाद उसे, one of the oldest surviving pieces of साहित्य in the English भाषा.
the आक्रमण on पर्ल Harbor ( पुकारा हवाई Operation or आपरेशन ai by the Japanese इम्पीरियल सामान्य मुख्यालय ( आपरेशन Z in नियोजन ) और the बैटल of Pearl हार्बर ) थी a आश्चर्य military strike conducted by the इम्पीरियल जापानी नेवी विरूद्ध the United States नवल आधार at Pearl हार्बर, हवाई, on the morning of दिसम्बर 7, 1941 ( दिसम्बर 8 in Japan ).
इससे the standpoint of the defenders, the आक्रमण commenced at 7:48 a.m. हवाई समय.
The attack थी intended as a निवारक कार्रवाई in अनुक्रम to रखना the u.S. Pacific बेड़े from दखल with सैन्य क्रियाएँ the साम्राज्य of जापानी was planning in southeast एशिया विरूद्ध overseas territories of the संयुक्त Kingdom, the नीदरलैंड्स, और the संयुक्त States.
The base was attacked by 353 Japanese सेनानी, बमवर्षक और torpedo planes in दो लहरें, शुभारम्भ from six aircraft वाहक.
सब eight u.S. Navy battleships were क्षतिग्रस्त, with four होने sunk.
दो of these were बाद उठाया, और साथ the बाकी four repaired, छह battleships returned to सेवा बाद in the युद्ध.
The जापानी भी sank or क्षतिग्रस्त तीन cruisers, तीन destroyers, an anti-aircraft प्रशिक्षण ship, और one minelayer.
188 u.S. aircraft were destroyed ; 2,402 Americans were मारे और 1,282 wounded.
महत्वपूर्ण base संस्थापना such as the शक्ति station, डॉकयार्ड, मेंटेनेंस, और ईंधन और torpedo storage सुविधाएं, as खूब as the submarine पियर और headquarters भवन ( भी home of the intelligence खण्ड ) were नहीं attacked.
जापानी नुकसान were लाइट : 29 वायुयान और five midget submarines lost, और 65 servicemen मारे or wounded.
एक जापानी नाविक थी captured.
The आक्रमण आए as a profound शॉक to the अमरीकी लोगों and led directly to the अमरीकी entry into World War ii in दोनो the प्रशांत and यूरोपीय थिएटर.
the following दिन ( दिसम्बर 8 ), the संयुक्त States declared war on जापानी.
घरेलू support लिये non-interventionism, जिससे था महरूम दमदार, disappeared.
Clandestine support of ब्रिटेन ( लिये example the neutrality पैट्रोल ) was replaced by active गठबंधन.
subsequent operations by the U.S. prompted जर्मनी और इटली to declare war on the u.S. on December 11, which was reciprocated by the u.S. the same day.
वहीँ यहूद numerous ऐतिहासिक precedents लिये unannounced सैन्य कार्रवाई by जापानी.
However, the कमी of कोई formal चेतावनी, विशेषकर while negotiations यहूद स्टिल apparently जारी, led President Franklin D. रूज़वेल्ट to proclaim दिसम्बर 7, 1941, `` a date जिससे will live in infamy ``.
u.S. Route 85 ( us 85 ) is a north–south संयुक्त States highway कि रनों लिये in the पहाड़ - उत्तरी मैदान states of the United States.
the southern टर्मिनस of the रूट is at the संयुक्त States-Mexico किनारा in El पासो, Texas, connecting with Mexican Federal Highway 45.
the उत्तरी terminus is at the United states-canada किनारा in fortuna, उत्तर डकोटा, जहाँ the रूट continues उत्तर as saskatchewan राजमार्ग 35.
In दोनो the संयुक्त राज्य और saskatchewan, कनाडा the route is known as the CanAm Highway.
Sections of us 85 हैं माना भाग of the थियोडोर Roosevelt एक्सप्रेसवे.
the United राज्य अध्यक्षीय election of 1968 was the 46th quadrennial अध्यक्षीय election, आयोजित on मंगलवार, November 5, 1968.
the Republican nominee, पूर्व vice-president Richard निक्सन, won the election over the Democratic nominee, incumbent Vice-President Hubert humphrey.
निक्सन भागा on a अभियान that promised to restore law and order to the स्वदेश 's शहरों, torn by riots और अपराधों.
विश्लेषकों have argued the election of 1968 is a realigning चुनाव as it permanently disrupted the नई Deal गठबन्धन कि था dominated अध्यक्षीय politics लिये 36 सालो.
Coming चार सालो after डेमोक्रेट lyndon B. जॉनसन won in a ऐतिहासिक भूस्खलन, the चुनाव saw the incumbent president forced आउट of the रेस और a रिपब्लिकन elected लिये the पहला समय in बारह सालो.
it was a विदारक national अनुभव, conducted दौरान a साल of हिंसा कि included the हत्या of सिविल rights नेता मार्टिन Luther किंग, Jr., और subsequent रेस riots across the स्वदेश, the assasination of लोकतांत्रिक अध्यक्षीय प्रत्याशी रॉबर्ट F. Kennedy, widespread विपक्ष to the वियतनाम युद्ध across विश्वविद्यालयों campuses, and हिंसक confrontations between पुलिस and anti-war प्रदर्शनकारियों at the 1968 Democratic नेशनल Convention as the Democratic पार्टी विभाजित again और again.
the चुनाव प्रदर्शित the strongest तीसरा पार्टी effort since 1912 by पूर्व अलबामा राज्यपाल जार्ज वालेस, a Democrat.
क्युकी Wallace 's campaign opposed federal intervention in the दक्षिण to end school segregation, he carried the गहन दक्षिण और भागा well in जातीय औद्योगिक जिले in the North.
इस was the पिछला election in जिससे नई York had the most मत in the चुनावी कॉलेज ( 43 votes ).
After the 1970 census, कैलिफ़ोर्निया gained the सबसे electoral votes और रै remained the most populous राज्य since then.
इस is the latest चुनाव जहाँ a presidential ticket won बगैर carrying the वाइस अध्यक्षीय प्रत्याशी 's home state.
Windows कार्य मैनेजर is a कार्य manager or प्रणाली मॉनिटर अनुप्रयोग शामिल साथ the Microsoft खिड़कियाँ nt परिवार of operating systems कि provides सीमित information about computer प्रदर्शन और running applications, processes और cpu उपयोग, कमिट चार्ज and मेमोरी सूचना, network कार्यकलाप और आंकडे, logged-in उपयोक्ता, and प्रणाली services ( और as प्रायः is the case with तन्त्र टूल्स provided by Microsoft लिये Windows, 3rd पार्टी तन्त्र is available जिससे भरता the आवश्यकताएँ more thoroughly, e.g, `` Process Explorer '', `` विस्तारित Task मैनेजर '', `` anvir Task मैनेजर '', `` प्रक्रम Hacker '', and `` प्रणाली Explorer '' ).
the Task मैनेजर can भी be used to नियत प्रक्रम priorities, प्रोसेसर affinity, forcibly terminate processes, और shut down, restart, hibernate or log बंद इससे खिड़कियाँ.

Kanji ( ; ) हैं the अपनाया logographic चाइनीज characters ( hanzi ) that are प्रयुक्त in the modern जापानी लिखने प्रणाली साथ with hiragana ( ひらがな, ), katakana ( カタカナ, ), Hindu-Arabic numerals, and the occasional उपयोग of the लैटिन वर्णमाला.
The जापानी term kanji ( ) लिये the Chinese characters literally अर्थात् `` Han characters '' और is लिखा using the same वर्ण as the Chinese hanzi ( ).

a सैन्य compass कि was used दौरान संसार युद्ध i.
A compass is a navigational instrument कि shows दिशानिर्देश in a फ़्रेम of सन्दर्भ कि is stationary सापेक्ष to the सतह of the धरती.
the frame of सन्दर्भ defines the four cardinal दिशानिर्देश ( or points ) – उत्तर, दक्षिण, ईस्ट, और वेस्ट.
Intermediate दिशानिर्देश हैं भी पारिभाषित.
Usually, a आरेख पुकारा a कम्पास रोज़, जिससे shows the directions ( with their names प्रायः abbreviated to आद्याक्षर ), is marked on the कम्पास.
जब the कम्पास is in उपयोग, the rose is aligned साथ the real दिशानिर्देश in the frame of सन्दर्भ, so, for example, the `` n '' चिह्नित on the रोज़ really points to the उत्तर.
Frequently, in जोड to the rose or sometimes बजाय of it, angle markings in degrees हैं shown on the कम्पास.
North corresponds to शून्य degrees, और the कोण बढ़ाएँ clockwise, so ईस्ट is 90 degrees, दक्षिण is 180, और वेस्ट is 270.
ये numbers allow the कम्पास to दिखाएँ azimuths or बियरिंग, which are commonly stated in this संकेतन.
The चुम्बकीय कम्पास was first invented as a यंत्र for divination as जल्दी as the चाइनीज हान राजवंश ( चूंकि परिचय 206 bc ).
The compass was प्रयुक्त in सोंग Dynasty China by the military लिये navigational orienteering by 1040-1044, और थी प्रयुक्त for maritime navigation by 1111 to 1117.
The उपयोग of a compass is अंकित in पश्चिमी यूरोपीय between 1187 और 1202, and in Persia in 1232.
the शुष्क compass was invented in Europe around 1300.
इस was supplanted in the जल्दी 20th सदी by the liquid-filled चुम्बकीय compass.
The इन्का Empire or inka Empire ( quechua : tawantinsuyu ) थी the largest empire in pre-columbian अमेरिका.
The प्रशासनिक, political और military center of the empire was स्तिथ in कुज़्को in modern-day Peru.
the Inca सभ्यता arose इससे the highlands of पेरू sometime in the early 13th सदी.
From 1438 to 1533, the incas प्रयुक्त a variety of विधि, from conquest to peaceful assimilation, to incorporate a विशाल portion of western South America, centered on the Andean पहाड़ ranges, सहित, besides पेरू, large parts of modern Ecuador, western and दक्षिण सेंट्रल बोलीविया, northwest Argentina, उत्तर और central Chile, और southern कोलंबिया into a राज्य comparable to the ऐतिहासिक empires of यूरेशिया.
the official language of the empire was Quechua, although hundreds of लोकल languages and dialects of quechua यहूद बोला.
the इन्का referred to their empire as Tawantinsuyu which can be translated as The चार regions or the चार संयुक्त प्रांतों.
वहीँ were many लोकल फ़ॉर्म of worship, most of उन्हें concerning लोकल पवित्र `` huacas ``, but the इन्का नेतृत्व encouraged the इबादत of inti —the सूर्य god—and imposed इसके sovereignty above अन्य cults such as that of Pachamama.
The Incas माना उनके किंग, the sapa Inca, to be the `` चाइल्ड of the सूर्य. ''
the गुर्दे are अंगों that serve अनेक essential नियामक roles in most animals, सहित vertebrates और कुछ invertebrates.
They are अनिवार्य in the urinary system and also serve homeostatic कृत्यों ऐसे as the विनियमन of इलेक्ट्रोलाइट्स, maintenance of acid–base balance, और regulation of रक्त pressure ( via maintaining नमक और water balance ).
They serve the देह as a natural filter of the blood, और हटाएँ wastes which हैं diverted to the urinary ब्लैडर.
In producing मूत्र, the गुर्दे excrete wastes ऐसे as यूरिया और ammonium, और they are भी जिम्मेदार लिये the reabsorption of जल, ग्लूकोज, और अमीनो acids.
the गुर्दे भी produce hormones including calcitriol, erythropoietin, और the enzyme renin.
Located at the rear of the abdominal cavity in the retroperitoneum, the kidneys प्राप्त रक्त इससे the युग्म renal धमनियों, और नाली into the paired renal रगों.
Each गुर्दा excretes मूत्र into a ureter, itself a paired ढांचा कि empties into the urinary ब्लैडर.
Renal physiology is the पढ़ाई of kidney function, जबकि nephrology is the चिकित्सा specialty चिंतित साथ गुर्दा रोगों.
Diseases of the गुर्दा are diverse, but individuals with kidney बीमारी frequently प्रदर्शक characteristic नैदानिक सुविधाएँ.
आम clinical conditions involving the kidney include the nephritic और nephrotic syndromes, renal cysts, अधि kidney चोट, दीर्घकालिक गुर्दा disease, urinary ट्रैक्ट संक्रमण, nephrolithiasis, and urinary tract obstruction.
Various cancers of the kidney exist ; the most common वयस्क renal कर्कट is renal कोशिका कार्सिनोमा.
Cancers, cysts, और कुछ other renal शर्तें can be प्रबंधित with हटाना of the kidney, or nephrectomy.
When renal function, measured by glomerular filtration रेट, is persistently ग़रीब, dialysis और kidney transplantation may be उपचार विकल्प.
Although वे हैं नहीं severely नुकसानदेह, kidney पत्थरों can be painful and a nuisance.
the removal of गुर्दा पत्थरों involves ultrasound उपचार to break up the पत्थरों into smaller टुकड़े, जिससे are then passed through the urinary ट्रैक्ट.
One आम लक्षण of kidney पत्थरों is a sharp पीड़ा in the medial/lateral खण्ड of the निम्नतर back.

लापरवाही ( lat. negligentia, इससे neglegere, to neglect, literally `` नहीं to चुनें up something '' ) is a विफलता to exercise the care that a reasonably prudent person होता कसरत in जैसे हालातों.
the area of अपकृत्य विधि known as लापरवाही involves नुक़सान caused by carelessness, नहीं intentional नुक़सान.
according to Jay M. feinman of the rutgers विश्वविद्यालयों स्कूल of विधि ;
`` The कोर विचार of negligence is कि लोगों चाहिए कसरत reasonable care जब वे अधिनियम by taking खाता of the potential harm कि they might foreseeably कारण नुक़सान to other people. ''
`` those जो go personally or bring प्रॉपर्टी जहाँ वे जान कि वे or it may come into टक्कर साथ the व्यक्तियों or प्रॉपर्टी of others have by law a duty डाल upon them to उपयोग reasonable परवाह और skill to avoid such a collision. ''
फ्लेचर v rylands ( [ 1866 ] LR 1 Ex 265 )
through civil वाद, if an injured person proves कि another व्यक्ति acted negligently to cause their चोट, they can रिकवर क्षतिपूर्ति to compensate for उनके नुक़सान.
proving a मामला लिये लापरवाही can potentially entitle the injured अभियोक्ता to मुआवजे लिये नुक़सान to उनके देह, प्रॉपर्टी, दिमागी well-being, वित्तीय औकात, or intimate संबंध.
however, क्युकी लापरवाही cases हैं बहुत fact-specific, इस सामान्य परिभाषा करता नहीं fully explain the अवधारणा of जब the law will require one person to compensate another for नुकसान caused by आकस्मिक चोट.
further, the law of negligence at common law is तभी एक पहलू of the law of देयता.
हालांकि resulting damages must be proven in अनुक्रम to रिकवर compensation in a negligence कार्रवाई, the प्रकृति और extent of those क्षतिपूर्ति हैं नहीं the प्राथमिक focus of negligence मामले.
A melanocytic nevus ( also ज्ञात as `` Nevocytic nevus '' ) is a प्रकार of lesion कि contains nevus कोशिकाएं ( a type of melanocyte ).
कुछ sources equate the पद mole साथ `` melanocytic nevus ''.
अन्य sources आरक्षित the term `` mole '' लिये अन्य purposes.
The बहुमत of moles appear during the पहला दो दशकों of a person’s life, जबकि about एक in प्रत्येक 100 शिशु is born साथ औज़ार.
Acquired moles हैं a रूप of benign neoplasm, जबकि जन्मजात moles, or जन्मजात nevi, हैं considered a नाबालिग malformation or hamartoma और may be at a higher रिस्क लिये melanoma.
a mole can be either subdermal ( अंतर्गत the skin ) or a pigmented विकास on the स्किन, formed mostly of a type of cell ज्ञात as a melanocyte.
the ऊँची विशेषज्ञता of the body’s pigmenting एजेंट, मेलेनिन, is जिम्मेदार लिये उनके dark रंग.
Moles हैं a सदस्य of the family of स्किन lesions ज्ञात as nevi.
the व्यापक metabolic फलक, or chemical स्क्रीन, ( CMP ; cpt code 80053 ) is a panel of 14 रक्त tests जिससे serves as an आरंभिक व्यापक चिकित्सा स्क्रीनिंग औजार.
The CMP provides a अशिष्ट जाँच of गुर्दा फलन, liver function, and electrolyte और द्रव balance, but it is far इससे पूर्ण.
असामान्य values इससे a cbc may be a परिणाम of गलत positives and thus the cbc may need to be repeated for a रोगी ( or replaced साथ a अधिक विशिष्ट परीक्षण ).
The cmp is an विस्तारित संस्करण of the मौलिक metabolic फलक ( bmp ), which does not शामिल जिगर परीक्षण.
a CMP ( or bmp ) can be ordered as भाग of a दिनचर्या शारीरिक परिक्षा, or may be used to monitor a patient साथ a chronic बीमारी, ऐसे as मधुमेह mellitus or hypertension.
Previous names लिये the फलक of परीक्षण have been chem 12, रसायन panel, रसायन स्क्रीन, sma 12, sma 20 and smac ( sequential Multiple विश्लेषण - Computer ).
the परीक्षण हैं performed on मशीने based on the AutoAnalyzer invented in 1957.
प्राकृतिक गैस extraction by देशों in घन मीटर प्रति साल.
Natural gas is a naturally occurring हाइड्रोकार्बन gas मिश्रण consisting primarily of मिथेन, लकिन commonly सहित varying amounts of अन्य hydrocarbons, कार्बन डाइऑक्साइड, नाइट्रोजन, और hydrogen sulfide.
प्राकृतिक gas is an energy source often प्रयुक्त लिये हीटिंग, कुकिंग, and विद्युत generation.
It is भी used as ईंधन for vehicles और as a chemical फर्टिलाइजर in the manufacture of प्लास्टिक and other commercially महत्वपूर्ण organic रसायन.
प्राकृतिक gas is found in गहन भूमिगत प्राकृतिक चट्टान formations or associated with अन्य हाइड्रोकार्बन reservoirs in कोयले beds और as methane clathrates.
पेट्रोलियम is भी another resource found in निकटता to and with प्राकृतिक गैस.
Most प्राकृतिक गैस थी निर्मित over समय by two mechanisms : biogenic and thermogenic.
biogenic gas is निर्मित by methanogenic organisms in marshes, bogs, landfills, और उथले sediments.
Deeper in the धरती, at वृहद temperature and pressure, thermogenic gas is निर्मित इससे buried सशुल्क material.
पहले natural गैस can be प्रयुक्त as a ईंधन, it जरूर undergo processing to हटाएँ impurities, सहित water, to meet the विशेषताएँ of marketable natural gas.
the by-products of प्रसंस्करण शामिल इथेन, प्रोपेन, butanes, pentanes, and उच्चतर molecular weight hydrocarbons, hydrogen sulfide ( which may be परिवर्तित into pure गंधक ), carbon डाइऑक्साइड, water वाष्प, और sometimes helium and नाइट्रोजन.
प्राकृतिक गैस is often informally referred to बस as गैस, विशेषकर when compared to other उर्जा sources such as oil or coal.

लिये सूचना परिचय the TV दिखाएँ अभिनीत the band, देखिए कल्पना मूवर्स ( tv श्रेणी ).

The platypus ( Ornithorhynchus anatinus ) is a semiaquatic स्तनधारी endemic to पूर्वी Australia, including तस्मानिया.
Together साथ the चार प्रजाति of एकिडना, it is one of the five extant प्रजाति of monotremes, the तभी mammals कि lay अंडे instead of giving जनम.
it is the एकमात्र जीना प्रतिनिधि of इसके परिवार ( ornithorhynchidae ) और genus ( ornithorhynchus ), though a number of सम्बन्धित प्रजाति have महरूम मिला in the fossil record.
The असामान्य रूप of इस egg-laying, बतख -billed, बीवर -tailed, otter -footed स्तनधारी मनोरथ European naturalists जब they first encountered it, साथ कुछ considering it an विस्तृत धोखाधड़ी.
it is one of the few विषैला mammals, the पुरूष platypus having a spur on the हिन्द पैर that delivers a venom सक्षम of causing severe पीड़ा to इंसानो.
The अद्वितीय सुविधाएँ of the platypus मेक it an महत्वपूर्ण subject in the study of evolutionary biology और a recognisable and iconic symbol of ऑस्ट्रेलिया ; it has appeared as a शुभंकर at national events और is featured on the reverse of इसके 20-cent coin.
The platypus is the एनिमल emblem of the राज्य of नई दक्षिण वेल्स.
जबतक the जल्दी 20th सदी, it was hunted for its फर, लकिन it is अभी protected throughout इसके दायरा.
हालांकि खिलाते प्रजनन programmes have था only सीमित कामयाबी और the platypus is vulnerable to the प्रभाव of प्रदूषण, it is not अंतर्गत कोई immediate threat.
The chupacabra or Chupacabras (, from chupar `` to suck '' and cabra `` बकरी '', वस्तुतः `` बकरी sucker '' ) is a legendary cryptid rumored to inhabit parts of the americas.

Physical descriptions of the प्राणी vary.

the North अमरीकी फ़्री व्यापार अनुबंध ( NAFTA ) is an agreement signed by कनाडा, मैक्सिको, और the संयुक्त राज्य, creating a trilateral trade bloc in उत्तर अमेरिका.
the अनुबंध आए into force on जनवरी 1, 1994.

थर्मल comfort is the condition of mind that expresses satisfaction with the थर्मल पर्यावरण और is assessed by subjective evaluation ( ansi / ashrae मानक 55 ).
Maintaining इस मानक of थर्मल comfort for occupants of buildings or other enclosures is एक of the महत्वपूर्ण लक्ष्य of HVAC ( हीटिंग, वेंटिलेशन, and एयर कंडीशनिंग ) डिज़ाइन engineers.
The Predicted Mean Vote ( pmv ) model स्टैंड among the सबसे recognized थर्मल सुकून मॉडल.
It was developed using सिद्धान्त of ऊष्मा संतुलन और प्रायोगिक data collected in a नियंत्रित जलवायु chamber अंतर्गत स्थिर state शर्तें.
क्युकी the PMV मॉडल थी निकला इससे आंकड़ा एकत्रित in a नियंत्रित जलवायु, it is नहीं उपयुक्त लिये applications in naturally ventilated स्पेसेस जिससे often have high स्तर of air गति.
इस shortcoming प्रेरित the विकास of a परिवार of empirical सांख्यिकीय मॉडल of थर्मल सुकून in naturally ventilated स्पेसेस ज्ञात as adaptive मॉडल.
अनुकूली मॉडल of थर्मल comfort consider occupants as dynamically interacting with उनके पर्यावरण, और controlling their थर्मल comfort by अर्थात् of clothing or window-opening और closing.
इस is in कंट्रास्ट to थर्मल सुकून in sealed इमारतें, in which occupants अनुभव the पर्यावरण passively.
Thermal सुकून is प्रभावित by ऊष्मा conduction, convection, विकिरण, और evaporative heat घाटा.
Thermal सुकून is कायम when the ऊष्मा generated by human metabolism is allowed to dissipate, यूँ maintaining थर्मल संतुलन with the परिवेश.
It has महरूम long पहचाना कि the सनसनी of अहसास hot or ठंडा is not just dependent on एयर temperature अलोन.
थर्मल comfort calculations according to ANSI/ASHRAE मानक 55 can be freely performed with the cbe थर्मल सुकून औजार लिये ashrae-55.
durante degli Alighieri, बस referred to as Dante (, ; ; c. 1265–1321 ), थी a major इतालवी poet of the Middle Ages.

मुख्यालय ( कोबे, जापानी )
( ) is a tire और रबर company based in Japan.
It is भाग of the Sumitomo Group.
the कम्पनी traces its origins to 1909, जब the sumitomo समूह बना an निवेश in dunlop जापानी, the newly formed Japanese subsidiary of the अंग्रेजों कम्पनी dunlop Rubber.
Over the सालो sumitomo and dunlop विकसित a close business संबंध, and in 1963 the Sumitomo Group acquired कंट्रोल of dunlop Japan and renamed it sumitomo Rubber उद्योग ltd.
in 1985, जब Dunlop रबर थी लिया over by btr पीएलसी, the कम्पनी acquired the ऑटोमोबाइल टायर assets of Dunlop, including the right to उपयोग the dunlop brand on ऑटोमोबाइल टायर.
the अधिग्रहण did नहीं शामिल the us और Australian व्यवसायों, which यहूद separately स्वामित्व, but in 1986 sumitomo also acquired the dunlop टायर निगम of the US from इसके प्रबन्धन.
In 1997, sumitomo formed a संयुक्त venture साथ goodyear Tire और Rubber Company, by जिससे goodyear and sumitomo सहमत to manufacture tires for प्रत्येक अन्य 's markets, सहित dunlop branded tires.

Today, the company makes a wide range of रबर आधारित उत्पाद, सहित ऑटोमोबाइल टायर, गोल्फ़ balls और tennis balls.

The Alps are एक of the ग्रेट mountain range systems of यूरोपीय stretching लगभग आरपार eight Alpine countries इससे Austria और स्लोवेनियाई in the east, स्विट्ज़रलैंड, Liechtenstein, जर्मनी, फ़्रांस to the वेस्ट and Italy and Monaco to the दक्षिण.
The kyu यहूद formed over सैंकड़ों of millions of सालो as the अफ़्रीकी और Eurasian tectonic प्लेटों collided.
चरम shortening caused by the event resulted in समुद्री sedimentary रॉक्स उठती by thrusting और फोल्डिंग into ऊँची पहाड़ चोटियों ऐसे as मोंट Blanc and the matterhorn.
Mont Blanc spans the French–Italian border, और at is the highest पहाड़ in the ऐल्प्स.
the अल्पाइन region क्षेत्रफल contains अनेक peaks उच्चतर than, known as the `` four-thousanders ``.
The ऊँचाई और size of the range affects the जलवायु in यूरोपीय ; in the kyu वर्षण levels vary greatly और climatic शर्तें consist of distinct zones.
Wildlife ऐसे as ibex live in the उच्चतर चोटियों to elevations of, and पौधे ऐसे as Edelweiss grow in rocky क्षेत्रों in निम्नतर elevations as खूब as in उच्चतर elevations.
Evidence of human habitation in the ऐल्प्स goes back to the paleolithic era.
a mummified man, संकल्पित to be 5,000 years बूढ़ा, was discovered on a हिमानी at the Austrian–Italian किनारा in 1991.
By the 6th सदी bc, the सेल्टिक la tène culture थी खूब स्थापित.
Hannibal may have crossed the Alps साथ a herd of हाथियों, और the romans था settlements in the प्रदेश.
In 1800 नेपोलियन crossed एक of the mountain गुजरता साथ an फौज of 40,000.
the 18th और 19th सदियां देखी an influx of naturalists, लेखक, और कलाकारों, in particular the romantics, followed by the सुनहरी आयु of alpinism as mountaineers began to ascend the चोटियों.
in World युद्ध II the तीसरा Reich invaded the अल्पाइन देशों, with the exception of स्विट्ज़रलैंड और liechtenstein ; Adolf हिटलर kept a base of operation in the bar ऐल्प्स throughout the युद्ध.
the अल्पाइन प्रदेश रै a दमदार सांस्कृतिक पहचान.
the परंपरागत culture of खेती, cheesemaking, और woodworking स्टिल exists in अल्पाइन गांवों, हालांकि the पर्यटक industry began to grow early in the 20th century और expanded greatly after World युद्ध ii to become the प्रबल industry by the end of the century.
the Winter ओलम्पिक खेल have महरूम hosted in the स्विस, फ्रेंच, इतालवी, Austrian and जर्मनी ऐल्प्स.
at present the प्रदेश is घर to 14 लाख people और रै 120 लाख सालाना visitors.

स्थान of the basque-language प्रांतों भीतर स्पेन और France
Basque ( endonym :, ) is the ancestral language of the Basque people, जो inhabit the बास्क Country, a प्रदेश spanning an क्षेत्रफल in northeastern स्पेन and southwestern France.
It is बोला by 27 % of basques in सब territories ( 714,136 आउट of 2,648,998 ).
of these, 663,035 सजीव in the Spanish भाग of the बास्क country and the बाकी 51,100 सजीव in the French भाग.
In अकादमिक चर्चाएँ of the distribution of बास्क in Spain और France, it is प्रथागत to refer to three प्राचीन प्रांतों in France and चार स्पेनी प्रांतों.
देशी speakers are concentrated in a संलग्न area सहित भाग of the स्पेनी autonomous समुदायों of the बास्क देश and नावारा और in the पश्चिमी हाफ of the फ्रेंच département of pyrénées-atlantiques.
the बास्क Autonomous Community is an administrative entity भीतर the binational ethnographic बास्क देश incorporating the traditional Spanish प्रांतों of biscay, gipuzkoa, and álava, जिससे retain their अस्तित्व as politico-administrative विभाजन.
ये प्रांतों and अनेक क्षेत्रों of Navarre are heavily populated by जातीय basques, लकिन Basque was, at तनिक until the 1990s, not spoken as a देशी language in most of álava, western parts of Biscay और सेंट्रल और दक्षिणी क्षेत्रों of नावारा, either because it था महरूम replaced by स्पेनी along the सदियां, in कुछ क्षेत्रों, or क्युकी it had never महरूम बोला there, in अन्य क्षेत्रों.
in southwestern France, the ancient basque-populated provinces यहूद labourd, Lower Navarre, and soule.
वे और other regions यहूद संचित into a single département in 1790 under the नाम Basses-Pyrénées, a नाम जिससे persisted जबतक 1970.
a standardized form of the Basque भाषा, called euskara Batua, थी developed by the बास्क भाषा अकादमी in the late 1960s.
euskara batua थी निर्मित so कि बास्क language could be used—and easily समझा by all Basque speakers—in औपचारिक परिस्थितियों ( शिक्षा, द्रव्यमान मीडिया, साहित्य ), and इस is इसके प्रमुख उपयोग today.
the भूमिका of इस मानक बास्क language depends on the भाषाई शैक्षणिक मॉडल of प्रत्येक region और each स्कूल.
in most areas of the स्पेनी बास्क देश, the शैक्षणिक Model d, where सब विषय are सिखाया in Basque, मगर `` स्पेनी भाषा और literature '' ( which is taught in Spanish ) is अभी the predominant model.
In फ़्रांस, the बास्क भाषा school seaska और the संघ लिये a दुभाषिया ( बास्क और फ्रेंच ) schooling Ikasbi मिलें a चौड़ी range of Basque भाषा शैक्षणिक needs up to the Sixth रूप, जबकि प्रायः struggling to surmount वित्तीय और प्रशासनिक constraints.
अलावा इससे this मानकीकृत संस्करण, वहीँ are five प्रमुख बास्क dialects : bizkaian, gipuzkoan, और Upper navarrese in स्पेन, और navarrese–lapurdian and Zuberoan ( in फ़्रांस ).

the अध्यक्ष, निर्देशकों और Company, of the बैंको of the संयुक्त States, commonly known as the First बैंको of the संयुक्त राज्य, was a सेंट्रल bank, चार्टर्ड for a पद of बीस years, by the संयुक्त राज्य Congress on फ़रवरी 25, 1791.

officially प्रस्तावित to the पहला सत्र of the पहला कॉंग्रेस in 1790, Hamilton 's बैंको faced widespread प्रतिरोध from opponents of increased संघीय शक्ति.

Purple पिया is a slang पद for a recreational ड्रग popular in the हिप hop जातियाँ in the southern संयुक्त States, originating in Houston, Texas.
इसके प्रमुख ingredient is नुस्खा -strength cough syrup containing codeine and promethazine.
खांसी सिरप is typically मिश्रित साथ ingredients such as Sprite नरम drink or Mountain Dew and टुकड़े of प्रसन्न rancher कैंडी.
The purplish वर्ण of purple drank आता from dyes in the cough syrup.
There हैं numerous कठबोली शर्तें लिये purple पिया, including sizzurp, झुकना, सिरप, drank, barre, जामुनी jelly, Texas चाय, और Tsikuni.
first/given, middle, and last/family/surname आरेख with J. S. बच as उदाहरण.
J. S. Bach shared his दिए नाम साथ six immediate परिवार members and many extended परिवार सदस्यों.
he shared उसके परिवार name with सबसे परिवार members.
A दिए name, in पश्चिमी contexts प्रायः referred to as a first नाम, is a personal नाम that specifies and differentiates between सदस्यों of a group of individuals, especially in a परिवार, all of जिनकी सदस्यों usually share the वही परिवार नाम ( surname ).
a दिए नाम is purposefully given, usually by a चाइल्ड 's parents at or निकट birth, in कंट्रास्ट to an inherited एक ऐसे as a family name.
a given नाम is sometimes legally changed through a name बदलें.
दिए names are often प्रयुक्त in a परिचित और friendly manner in अनौपचारिक situations.
in अधिक औपचारिक परिस्थितियों the उपनाम is used instead, जबतक it is necessary to distinguish between लोगों साथ the same surname.
The मुहावरा `` on a first-name आधार '' ( or `` on first-name terms '' ) alludes to the familiarity of addressing another by a दिए name.
the western स्टाइल of having दोनो a परिवार name ( surname ) और a given name is far इससे सार्वभौमिक.
In अनेक देशों it is आम लिये ordinary लोगों to have तभी एक नाम ( a mononym ).
हाइड्रोक्लोरिक acid is a साफ, colourless solution of hydrogen chloride ( h Cl ) in जल.
it is a अत्यधिक corrosive, strong खनिज acid साथ अनेक industrial उपयोग.
Hydrochloric एसिड is found naturally in gastric एसिड.
historically पुकारा muriatic acid, and आत्माओं of नमक, हाइड्रोक्लोरिक acid थी produced from vitriol ( sulfuric एसिड ) and आम salt.
it पहला appeared दौरान the पुनर्जागरण, and then it was प्रयुक्त by chemists such as glauber, Priestley और Davy in their scientific research.
With major उत्पादन starting in the Industrial Revolution, हाइड्रोक्लोरिक एसिड is used in the रासायनिक उद्योग as a रासायनिक अभिकर्मक in the large-scale उत्पादन of vinyl chloride for PVC plastic, और MDI / tdi for polyurethane.

गेहूं ( Triticum spp. ) is a खाद्यान्न अनाज, originally from the levant region of the Near East और ethiopian हाइलैंड्स, लकिन अभी cultivated worldwide.
in 2010, संसार उत्पादन of गेहूं was 651 million टन, making it the third most-produced खाद्यान्न बाद मक्का ( 844 million tons ) and rice ( 672 लाख टन ).
गेहूं थी the second most-produced खाद्यान्न in 2009 ; world production in कि साल थी 682 million tons, बाद मक्का ( 817 million टन ), और साथ rice as a close third ( 679 लाख टन ).
इस अनाज is grown on अधिक जमीन क्षेत्रफल than any अन्य commercial खाना.
संसार trade in wheat is वृहद than for सब other crops combined.
Globally, गेहूं is the अग्रणी source of सब्ज़ी प्रोटीन in इंसान खाना, having a higher protein सामग्री than soybeans or the other major cereals, maize ( corn ) or राइस.
in शर्तें of कुल उत्पादन tonnages used लिये food, it is currently दूसरी to राइस as the प्रमुख human खाना क्रॉप and ahead of मक्का, after allowing for maize 's अधिक extensive use in एनिमल फ़ीड्स.
गेहूं थी a कुंजी फ़ैक्टर enabling the emergence of city-based societies at the प्रारंभ of सभ्यता क्युकी it थी one of the first फसलों that could be easily cultivated on a large scale, and had the additional लाभ of yielding a कटाई that provides long-term storage of खाना.
गेहूं contributed to the emergence of city-states in the fertile Crescent, सहित the babylonian और Assyrian empires.
Wheat grain is a स्टेपल खाना प्रयुक्त to मेक flour लिये leavened, flat and steamed breads, बिस्कुट, कुकीज़, cakes, नाश्ता खाद्यान्न, पास्ता, नूडल्स, couscous and for fermentation to मेक बियर, other alcoholic पेय, or biofuel.
गेहूं is planted to a सीमित extent as a forage crop लिये livestock, और इसके स्ट्रॉ can be used as a निर्माण material for roofing thatch.
the पूरे grain can be milled to leave बस the endosperm लिये श्वेत flour.
the by-products of इस हैं चोकर और रोगाणु.
the पूरे अनाज is a concentrated source of विटामिन, minerals, और प्रोटीन, while the परिष्कृत grain is mostly मंड.

the धर्मं व्हील, often प्रयुक्त to represent the प्रतिष्ठित eightfold Path
The Noble eightfold Path (, ) is एक of the principal शिक्षाओं of the Buddha, जो वर्णित it as the रास्ता अग्रणी to the cessation of कष्ट ( dukkha ) and the उपलब्धि of self-awakening.
It is used to develop इनसाइट into the true प्रकृति of phenomena ( or वास्तविकता ) and to eradicate greed, hatred, and भ्रांति.
The Noble eightfold पाथ is the चौथी of the Buddha 's चार प्रतिष्ठित सच्चाई ; the first element of the प्रतिष्ठित eightfold पाथ is, in turn, an understanding of the Four Noble सच्चाई.
It is also known as the मध्य पाथ or Middle Way.
सब eight elements of the पाथ begin साथ the word `` right '', which translates the शब्द samyañc ( in संस्कृत ) or sammā ( in pāli ).
These denote पूर्णता, togetherness, और coherence, और can भी सुझाएँ the होश of `` पूर्ण '' or `` आदर्श ''.
'samma ' is also अनूदित as `` wholesome '', `` हिकमत '' और `` skillful ''.
in Buddhist प्रतीकवाद, the प्रतिष्ठित eightfold Path is प्रायः represented by means of the dharma व्हील ( dharmachakra ), जिनकी आठ तीलियां represent the eight तत्व of the path.
The Grammy Award लिये सोंग of the साल is an सम्मान प्रस्तुत at the Grammy पुरस्कार, a रस्म कि थी स्थापित in 1958 और originally called the Gramophone पुरस्कार.
पुरस्कार in several श्रेणी are वितरित annually by the National अकादमी of रिकॉर्डिंग Arts and Sciences of the संयुक्त राज्य to `` honor कलाकारी उपलब्धि, technical proficiency और overall excellence in the रिकॉर्डिंग उद्योग, बगैर लिहाज़ to album बिक्री or chart position. ''
अर्थशास्त्र is the social विज्ञान that analyzes the उत्पादन, वितरण, and खपत of goods and सेवाएं.
The पद अर्थशास्त्र comes from the प्राचीन यूनानी ( ', `` प्रबन्धन of a household, administration '' ) from ( ', `` हाउस '' ) + ( ', `` कस्टम '' or `` law '' ), hence `` rules of the हाउस ( hold ) ''.
Political economy थी the earlier name for the subject, लकिन economists in the लेट 19th सदी suggested `` economics '' as a shorter पद लिये `` economic science '' that भी avoided a सीमित political-interest connotation और as समान in form to `` गणित ``, `` ethics '', और so forth.
a फ़ोकस of the विषय is how आर्थिक agents व्यवहार or interact और how economies कार्य.
सतत with this, a प्राथमिक textbook distinction is between microeconomics and macroeconomics.
microeconomics examines the behavior of मौलिक elements in the economy, सहित individual एजेंटों ( ऐसे as households और firms or as खरीदार and विक्रेता ) और बाज़ार, and their interactions.
macroeconomics analyzes the entire economy and issues affecting it, सहित बेरोजगारी, महंगाई, economic growth, और मौद्रिक and fiscal नीति.
अन्य व्यापक भेद include those between धनात्मक economics ( describing `` कया is '' ) और normative अर्थशास्त्र ( वकालत `` कया ought to be '' ) ; between आर्थिक सिद्धान्त और applied अर्थशास्त्र ; between तर्कसंगत and behavioral अर्थशास्त्र ; और between मुख्यधारा economics ( अधिक `` परंपरागत '' और dealing with the `` rationality-individualism-equilibrium nexus '' ) और heterodox अर्थशास्त्र ( अधिक `` radical '' और dealing with the `` institutions-history-social structure nexus '' ).
आर्थिक विश्लेषण may be लागू throughout समाज, as in कारोबार, वित्त, स्वास्थ्य परवाह, और सरकारी, लकिन also to ऐसे diverse subjects as अपराधों, शिक्षा, the family, law, राजनीती, धर्म, सोशल संस्थानों, युद्ध, और विज्ञान.
at the turn of the 21st सदी, the expanding डोमेन of अर्थशास्त्र in the social sciences रै महरूम described as economic साम्राज्यवाद.
an increasing क्रमांक of economists have called for increased जोर on पर्यावरणीय sustainability ; this क्षेत्रफल of शोध is known as ecological अर्थशास्त्र.

the ड्रग or अन्य substance रै a low संभावित for गाली relative to the दवाएँ or other substances in अनुसूची III.
the ड्रग or अन्य पदार्थ रै a currently स्वीकृत चिकित्सा use in उपचार in the संयुक्त राज्य.

मध्य us household आय, 2001-2011
household आय is a measure commonly used by the संयुक्त राज्य सरकारी और निजी संस्थानों.
Each household is measured by the income of प्रत्येक resident over the age of 15.
आय शामिल मजदूरी and salaries, बेरोजगारी बीमे, विकलांगता भुगतान, child support payments received, नियमित rental रसीदें, as खूब as कोई निजी business, investment, or अन्य kinds of आय received routinely.
While inflation-adjusted ( `` real '' ) household आय had been increasing लगभग every साल इससे 1945 to 1999, it has since been चपटा और even decreased recently.
U.S. मध्य household आय गिरी from $ 51,144 in 2010 to $ 50,502 in 2011.
Extreme गरीबी in the संयुक्त राज्य, अर्थ households living on कम than $ 2 प्रति दिन पहले सरकारी benefits, doubled from 1996 to 1.5 million households in 2011, including 2.8 लाख children.
The residents of the household do नहीं have to be सम्बन्धित to the सिर of the household लिये their earnings to be माना part of the household 's आय.
As households tend to share a समान आर्थिक कॉन्टेक्स्ट, the उपयोग of household income remains among the सबसे widely accepted measures of आय.
कि the आकार of a household is नहीं commonly taken into account in such measures may विकृत कोई विश्लेषण of fluctuations भीतर or among the household आय श्रेणी, and may रेंडर सीधा comparisons between quintiles मुश्किल or even नामुमकिन.
The lapse rate is पारिभाषित as the rate of decrease साथ ऊँचाई for an atmospheric variable.
The variable शामिल is तापमान unless specified otherwise.
The शब्दावली arises इससे the word बीतने in the sense of a घटी or मनाही.
जबकि most often applied to Earth 's माहौल the concept can be विस्तारित to कोई gravitationally supported बॉल of गैस.

Its best-known hardware उत्पाद are the मैक लकीर of कंप्यूटर, the ipod music खिलाड़ी, the iphone स्मार्टफोन, and the iPad टैब्लेट computer.
Its तन्त्र includes the OS X और आईओएस ऑपरेटिंग systems, the iTunes मीडिया browser, the Safari web ब्राउजर, and the iLife और iwork रचनात्मकता और production suites.
The कम्पनी थी संस्थापित on April 1, 1976, and incorporated as ठहराना Computer, Inc. on जनवरी 3, 1977.

खण्ड 8 housing in the दक्षिण bronx
Section 8 of the आवास अधिनियम of 1937 ( ), प्रायः simply ज्ञात as Section 8, as repeatedly amended, authorizes the payment of rental आवास assistance to निजी जमींदार on निमित्त of लगभग 3.1 लाख low-income households.
it operates through अनेक कार्यक्रम, the largest of which, the आवास चुनाव Voucher program, pays a विशाल portion of the rents और utilities of about 2.1 लाख households.
the us विभाग of आवास और शहरी विकास manages the खण्ड 8 कार्यक्रम.
The Housing Choice वाउचर Program provides `` tenant-based '' rental assistance, so a किरायेदार can move इससे one ईकाई of at तनिक minimum housing विशेषता to another.
It also allows individuals to लागू उनके monthly voucher towards the खरीदें of a home, with over $ 17 अरब going towards such purchases each साल ( from ncsha.org विश्लेषण ).
the maximum allowed voucher is $ 2200 a माह.
खण्ड 8 भी authorizes a किस्में of `` project-based '' rental assistance programs, अंतर्गत which the मालिक reserves कुछ or all of the इकाई in a भवन लिये low-income tenants, in वापसी for a संघीय government guarantee to मेक up the अंतर between the किरायेदार 's योगदान और the किराया लिये 1 cent in the मालिक 's contract with the सरकारी.
A किरायेदार जो leaves a subsidized प्रोजेक्ट will lose अभिगम to the project-based subsidy.
the संयुक्त राज्य विभाग of आवास and शहरी विकास and United राज्य विभाग of Veterans अफेयर्स have a special Section 8 कार्यक्रम called VASH ( दिग्गजों अफेयर्स supportive Housing ), or hud-vash, जिससे देता आउट a certain क्रमांक of खण्ड 8 वाउचर to eligible homeless और वरना vulnerable US हथियारबंद forces दिग्गजों.
